INSERT INTO tableName (id, author_id, words, tags, created_at, updated_at) VALUES
	('387830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca6', 'The world continues to offer glittering prizes to those who have stout hearts and sharp swords.', '"World,Sharp,Offer"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca6', '"Good God, do you mean to say this place is a club?"', '"God,Good,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"Creativity is a mansion. If you\'re empty in one room, all you have to do is go out into the hallway and enter another room that\'s full."', '"Creativity,Room,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I taught a master class in film in France, and that was a great experience because I got a chance to study the French film culture and the French film history, so to add... just to expand myself just personally and professionally was really helpful."', '"History,Experience,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"When you look at someone good like J.J. Abrams who gives you the spectacle and great action set pieces but also gives you character and great story and plotting and narrative, I think it\'s my job - and my intention - to do both."', '"Good,Great,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"My parents separated when I was 2, and my dad always lived in Chicago and my mother in L.A. I\'d go back and forth and sometimes spend the summer with my dad, but L.A. was home."', '"Home,Dad,Summer"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', 'Success is really about your mindset.', '"Success,Mindset,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I\'m single-minded. When I\'m working on a project, all my attention is there."', '"Attention,Project,Single-Minded"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I was a little hesitant at first because there\'s so many ways you can get \'Straight Outta Compton\' wrong. You know, it\'s such a great story; it\'s such a classic tale. I was a little nervous \'cause it\'s like a very narrow road to success with that type of story - you got to get it right - but when I read it, I was pleasantly surprised."', '"Success,Great,Road"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', 'I don\'t have a typical filmmaker background. I didn\'t grow up with a super eight camera or a video camera. I didn\'t start cutting movies when I was four or five.', '"Movies,Grow,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I was doing well in TV as a freelance cameraman, but it wasn\'t the direction I wanted to go in. I directed videos and tried to put something cinematic in every one. Dialogue, action sequences, helicopter, Steadicam."', '"Action,Direction,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"Why did I want to become a director? I just had an early interest. My uncle was an actor in a local community theatre, and he ultimately persuaded me and a buddy of mine to come to that theatre, and we went to meet girls, and that turned into interested in kind of behind-the-scenes things, and from that point on, I was focused."', '"Community,Me,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"When you start directing movies at the age of 24, you\'re just a kid; you don\'t necessarily even have the experiences to add to the story. You\'re working off of instinct and raw emotions and raw talent, and hopefully it\'s the same trajectory as growing as a person."', '"Age,Movies,Talent"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I know a lot of people who enjoy rap music who aren\'t black. You can\'t just say it\'s black music. To segregate films the way Hollywood likes to segregate films, ultimately everyone loses."', '"Music,Black,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I\'m not afraid of a big studio film; I trust my instincts. But for me, it\'s not really about box office. It\'s about looking back on your work and not having to apologize for it."', '"Work,Trust,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I actually didn\'t really start to get into the research of film until I was much older. I decided I wanted to direct a lot earlier than I started to do the research, which is really strange, but it is the case."', '"Research,Start,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I remember where I was when I first heard \'Boyz N The Hood\' - 126th Street and Normandy, South Central, Los Angeles. I remember that I was on my porch. What they described in that song was so vivid and so clear to me because it was the kind of life I was used to witnessing and partly experiencing in my neighborhood."', '"Life,Me,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I knew that in Hollywood they tend to pigeonhole talent, and when you experience a little success in one genre, their instinct is to keep you in that box."', '"Success,Experience,Talent"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I love a challenge. So when I did \'Friday,\' I didn\'t want to do another comedy back-to-back. With \'Set It Off,\' that was a little different from \'The Negotiator\' and \'The Italian Job.\' So for me, it\'s all about challenge. It\'s all about challenge and about just learning."', '"Love,Learning,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"\'Straight Outta Compton\' is my first biopic, my first period piece, and I got a chance to kind of get out there like some of my idols, you know, like Scorsese, Spielberg, Spike Lee, the guys who came before me. You know, I\'m feeling good about it."', '"Good,Chance,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', 'Everybody comes to film differently; everybody has different backgrounds. Just find whatever your lane is naturally. Don\'t try to force yourself into someone else\'s vision or try to tell a story that you\'re not passionate about.', '"Vision,Yourself,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I take nothing away from my existence in the \'hood, because it sharpened my instincts. We had a different way of living that developed our survival instincts, and I use those to this day when I make films. You can\'t buy that."', '"Day,Way,Survival"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', 'You have to enjoy yourself when you go to the movies. People don\'t want to spend their hard earned money to simply go see a history lesson.', '"History,Money,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', 'Hip hop has been an integral part of my life and my whole career. I started off doing videos with Ice Cube and Dre and Mary J. Blige and TLC.', '"Life,My Life,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"We didn\'t have much money growing up, so we hopped around L.A. a lot in the \'70s, \'80s and \'90s. I\'m very familiar with the shifting culture there."', '"Money,Culture,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"If I were to do a movie about Apollo 13, I\'d be at NASA studying what it took to go into space. It\'s part of your job to go deep, to interview the right people."', '"Space,People,Right People"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I always direct next to the camera and watch my actors, and so you can see the small things that you can\'t see on the small screen but you can definitely see on the big screen."', '"Small Things,See,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"I never limit myself when it comes to telling stories; I think people can see that in my body of work. It\'s just about, \'What\'s a great story? Is it unique? Is it a challenge?\'"', '"Work,Great,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"No matter where you came from, you can be inspired."', '"Matter,Where,Inspired"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"Most of music videos were short films - they had dialogue, action sequences. I shot with cranes and helicopters. I wanted to created cinema-like moments."', '"Music,Action,Shot"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca7', '"What do I bring to a film? I think, maybe, I know for a fact that I focus on connection of character; I focus on warmth and a heart, but I don\'t know if it\'s because I\'m African American or because I\'m crazy -who knows."', '"Focus,Heart,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'Metaphysics is the finding of bad reasons for what we believe upon instinct; but to find these reasons is no less an instinct.', '"Believe,Bad,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'True penitence condemns to silence. What a man is ready to recall he would be willing to repeat.', '"Silence,Man,True"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"The world is the best of all possible worlds, and everything in it is a necessary evil."', '"Best,World,Evil"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'The one self-knowledge worth having is to know one\'s own mind.', '"Mind,Know,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'The secret of happiness is to admire without desiring. And that is not happiness.', '"Happiness,Admire,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"Our live experiences, fixed in aphorisms, stiffen into cold epigrams. Our heart\'s blood, as we write it, turns to mere dull ink."', '"Heart,Live,Blood"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'Adam knew Eve his wife and she conceived. It is a pity that this is still the only knowledge of their wives at which some men seem to arrive.', '"Knowledge,Men,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"We say that a girl with her doll anticipates the mother. It is more true, perhaps, that most mothers are still but children with playthings."', '"Children,True,Doll"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"The mood in which my book was conceived and executed, was in fact to some extent a passing one."', '"Mood,Book,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'Eclecticism - every truth is so true that any truth must be false.', '"Truth,True,Truth Is"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"It is good to know what a man is, and also what the world takes him for. But you do not understand him until you have learnt how he understands himself."', '"Good,Man,World"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'Another occupation might have been better.', '"Better,Been,Another"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"It is by a wise economy of nature that those who suffer without change, and whom no one can help, become uninteresting. Yet so it may happen that those who need sympathy the most often attract it the least."', '"Nature,Change,Sympathy"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"There are persons who, when they cease to shock us, cease to interest us."', '"Us,Interest,Shock"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', '"One said of suicide, As long as one has brains one should not blow them out. And another answered, But when one has ceased to have them, too often one cannot."', '"Suicide,Long,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'The man who has ceased to fear has ceased to care.', '"Fear,Man,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'There are those who so dislike the nude that they find something indecent in the naked truth.', '"Truth,Naked,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'The deadliest foe to virtue would be complete self-knowledge.', '"Virtue,Complete,Foe"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca8', 'The force of the blow depends on the resistance. It is sometimes better not to struggle against temptation. Either fly or yield at once.', '"Struggle,Fly,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', 'And how is clarity to be achieved? Mainly by taking trouble and by writing to serve people rather than to impress them.', '"People,Clarity,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', 'Poetry had far better imply things than preach them directly... in the open pulpit her voice grows hoarse and fails.', '"Poetry,Better,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"The most emphatic place in a clause or sentence is the end. This is the climax; and, during the momentary pause that follows, that last word continues, as it were, to reverberate in the reader\'s mind. It has, in fact, the last word."', '"Mind,Pause,End"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"A man can make himself put down what comes, even if it seems nauseating nonsense; tomorrow some of it may not seem wholly nonsense at all."', '"Tomorrow,Man,Nonsense"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"Apart from a few simple principles, the sound and rhythm of English prose seem to me matters where both writers and readers should trust not so much to rules as to their ears."', '"Trust,Simple,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"At Munich we sold the Czechs for a few months grace, but the disgrace will last as long as history."', '"History,Grace,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', 'Most style is not honest enough.', '"Style,Enough,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"The only hope I can see for the future depends on a wiser and braver use of the reason, not a panic flight from it."', '"Hope,Future,See"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fca9', '"The two World Wars came in part, like much modern literature and art, because men, whose nature is to tire of everything in turn... tired of common sense and civilization."', '"Nature,Men,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', 'Can any of you seriously say the Bill of Rights could get through Congress today? It wouldn\'t even get out of committee.', '"Today,Seriously,Committee"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', 'I can get a firestorm going anywhere in the United States by saying \'O.J.\'', '"I Can,Saying,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', 'I use the rules to frustrate the law. But I didn\'t set up the ground rules.', '"Law,Rules,Ground"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', '"I would strongly recommend any young man to stay away from criminal law. It\'s not a good place to be, unfortunately."', '"Good,Man,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', '"Among the rednecks of America, which there are many more than people seem to realize, it was terribly damaging. I got blamed for O.J.\'s acquittal."', '"America,People,Realize"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', '"Justice Scalia is predictable. He can be counted on to come down with a conservative opinion, and generally, to bring Justice Clarence Thomas with him."', '"Justice,Opinion,Conservative"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', '"I enjoy personal injury cases. I\'ve tried quite a few of those. And, frankly, any kind of litigation that is trouble-shooting, whether it\'s equities, suits and injunctions, or whatever."', '"Whatever,Enjoy,Injury"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', 'There are no major cities I haven\'t been in - at least once. I\'d be just as happy not to go out of town for a couple of months and play with toys.', '"Toys,Happy,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaa', '"If I\'m offered a good case in Florida or a good case somewhere else, South Florida will win every time."', '"Time,Good,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I\'m passionate about politics, but when it comes to political parties, I\'m despondent. I\'m disappointed at the absence of a sense of humanity and struggle to not become a cynic."', '"Politics,Struggle,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I think creativity is spiritual. I absolutely believe that.', '"Believe,Spiritual,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:34:00', '2023-05-29 11:34:00'),
	('387900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"No matter all of your credits and accomplishments - you can be forgotten in a trice. The idea that you have to go back and start again after considerable success can destroy you if you\'re not strong. I never lost track of who I am and what I can do, because I continually find things to do, but not everyone has that resource."', '"Success,I Am,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"There is one confrontation scene toward the end of the picture. In the middle of the scene, I thought, That\'s Sean Connery! I don\'t know how else to describe Sean Connery. I still feel that way."', '"Way,Feel,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I always play these bad guys, and I\'m really a nice guy."', '"Bad,Always,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I can\'t pretend at how much I object to all of the plays that keep being brought back over and over again, the so-called classic plays. I mean how many times can we see \'The Glass Menagerie?\'"', '"Back,See,Glass"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"Arnold Schwarzenegger, I don\'t know if you\'d call him a great actor, but he\'s amazing in terms of his presence, and he is interesting enough that you want to watch him."', '"Great,Amazing,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"After I finished school, I headed for Los Angeles, thinking, \'Movies. Beaches.\' But I wanted to do serious stage work, so I upped sticks and moved to New York to study. I did the usual day jobs to support myself - waiting on tables, washing dishes, parking cars, anything to pay the rent. I was a terrible waiter, by the way."', '"Work,Movies,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I\'m just having a wonderful time. It\'s an interesting thing that I\'m very comfortable with this material and I don\'t know why. Maybe it\'s because I did MacBeth.', '"Time,Know,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"All the stuff that you visualized that was going to work so beautifully, you discover is trashed, so you jump to something else."', '"Work,Jump,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'The difficulty is capturing surprise on film.', '"Surprise,Film,Difficulty"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'People desire power. I don\'t know why they want it so. It seems to me it implies a hugely superior intellect which separates them from most of the populace.', '"Power,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I\'m not going to just say nice things about everybody unless I mean it.', '"Nice,Mean,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'Woody Allen sets are very quiet. Extraordinary sense of power from a man who doesn\'t do anything except just stand there.', '"Power,Man,Stand"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I really like to experiment. That\'s the only way I can work. It\'s instinctive.', '"Work,Way,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I just throw it out and see what happens. If it sounds and feels right, then I continue."', '"See,Continue,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"There are certain men and women who, from the minute they step in front of a camera, that\'s exactly where they belong. Connery\'s one."', '"Women,Men,Step"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"With Connery, he does act. He is in complete command. He completely trusts the person first, then the instrument. I\'ve worked with his son also, on a picture in Russia."', '"Picture,Son,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I\'d like President Bush to think maybe there\'s another way to think, that maybe Kissinger was wrong when he says we had to go in there because he was wrong about Vietnam."', '"Way,Wrong,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"If these men decided that they have to go in there and fight, I want them to send their own children and grandchildren. I want them to not send a bunch of strangers\' kids in there to fight and die."', '"Men,Fight,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I\'d like President Bush to get a gun in his hands. I\'ll go with him. I can\'t think of anything better than to die in place \'s just beginning their lives.', '"Gun,Die,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I trust that the president will try, just give it one more shot, some revolutionary way of not doing this, of bringing all those kids back home safely."', '"Trust,Home,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"The idea that you can make love and not war really is pretty neat. That thing in Korea, the thing in Israel - that\'s all over the world. There must be a new way of thinking."', '"Love,War,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I have two brothers buried in the military cemetery in Texas. I don\'t want to see any more of that.', '"See,More,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I don\'t want to talk in terms of miracles. I think this is a very serious situation. But I do want to talk in terms of Bush becoming a man of the hour, and I think this is way to do it."', '"Man,Way,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I acted my heart out.', '"Heart,Out,Acted"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"Milos said, You\'re my first choice. From my point of view, that doesn\'t pay the rent. I said, Tell me what I have to do next because I\'m busy painting my kitchen."', '"Busy,View,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"Suddenly I was the man who got the part that every actor in the English language was trying to get. I was really scared. I had talked the talk, and now I had to walk the walk. For three days, I couldn\'t answer the phone."', '"Walk,Man,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"As much preparation as I had made for the old man Salieri, gestures and so on, the fact is after sitting for hours, your movements are kind of slow."', '"Man,Preparation,Old Man"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'Once I looked into a mirror at my face I felt like it was completely convincing. I was Salieri.', '"Mirror,Face,Once"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I\'m a very proud actor.', '"Proud,Actor,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"With Dick Smith there, and the words of Peter Shaffer... they\'ve got to be the most beautiful descriptions in music ever written on film or in literature. And we could hear the music accompanying the words... What more can you ask for?"', '"Music,Most Beautiful,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I love parties. I love a good time.', '"Love,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"Whenever there were parties, I wasn\'t invited because I began to be like that character. In a way, that contributed to the success of the performance."', '"Success,Character,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I worked with Harold Pinter once as my first Broadway show. It was one of the most exciting things that ever happened to me.', '"Me,First,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I\'m the spokesperson for the Multifaith Alliance for Syrian Refugees. My father was from Syria. It\'s an American initiative, and it\'s multi-faith. So, it\'s maybe 60-65 different organisations, Jews, Christians, Hindus... Anyway, it\'s very important and serious."', '"Father,Important,Serious"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I\'m first-generation American - my people came over on boats - and I think it\'s a shame to close the door on people who really need freedom.', '"Freedom,Door,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'One of the great values of the theater is a communal search for truth; I believe that sincerely.', '"Truth,Great,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', 'I cannot imagine not working. I don\'t understand the word \'retirement.\'', '"Retirement,Understand,Imagine"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"My Oscar has appeared in every play I\'ve done since - not in view of the audience, but for my colleagues to enjoy."', '"Colleagues,View,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I\'m not afraid to go anywhere, to the smallest theatre or the least amount of money."', '"Money,Go,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"There are real tricks to getting a job that I just don\'t like or understand - it feels too close to pandering. I\'ve tried it, but it doesn\'t work."', '"Work,Real,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"It sounds funny, but I felt that my responsibility as an American actor was to let the British know we can act as well as they can."', '"Funny,Responsibility,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"The only reason I signed on for a speech and drama course was because I thought it would be easy, but as soon as I stepped on the stage, I thought, \'This is exactly where I belong.\'"', '"Drama,Easy,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I\'m a comedian at heart, and I really can make people laugh, but ever since \'Amadeus,\' all I seem to do is play dramatic roles and villains."', '"Heart,People,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"My family is blue-collar - coal miners and steelworkers. My father was an automobile mechanic, and us boys were brought up to work. I used to pump gasoline at 11 cents a gallon. I thought I would like to be a first-rate mechanic; a respected, hard-working man."', '"Work,Family,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"Marlon Brando was the major influence in my life, though I never met him. And my father - we didn\'t get along, but he was an influence in terms of honesty and work ethic. That\'s the greatest compliment I could pay him."', '"Life,Work,Honesty"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcab', '"I like to teach. And when I spot talent without ambition, it makes me angry. I give students short shrift if they\'re not willing to do the work. Relying on talent is not enough."', '"Work,Angry,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'The test of a first-rate intelligence is the ability to hold two opposed ideas in mind at the same time and still retain the ability to function.', '"Time,Intelligence,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"First you take a drink, then the drink takes a drink, then the drink takes you."', '"New Years,Drink,First"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Show me a hero and I\'ll write you a tragedy.', '"Hero,Me,Tragedy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Never confuse a single defeat with a final defeat.', '"Never,Defeat,Final"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Personality is an unbroken series of successful gestures.', '"Personality,Gestures,Successful"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'There are no second acts in American lives.', '"American,Second,Lives"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"In a real dark night of the soul, it is always three o\'clock in the morning, day after day."', '"Morning,Night,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"You don\'t write because you want to say something, you write because you have something to say."', '"Because,Want,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Family quarrels are bitter things. They don\'t go according to any rules. They\'re not like aches or wounds, they\'re more like splits in the skin that won\'t heal because there\'s not enough material."', '"Family,Skin,Rules"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Vitality shows in not only the ability to persist but the ability to start over.', '"Inspirational,Start,Ability"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Life is essentially a cheat and its conditions are those of defeat; the redeeming things are not happiness and pleasure but the deeper satisfactions that come out of struggle.', '"Life,Happiness,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Genius is the ability to put into effect what is on your mind.', '"Communication,Mind,Genius"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'It is sadder to find the past again and find it inadequate to the present than it is to have it elude you and remain forever a harmonious conception of memory.', '"Sad,Past,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"There are only the pursued, the pursuing, the busy and the tired."', '"Busy,Tired,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"I\'m a romantic; a sentimental person thinks things will last, a romantic person hopes against hope that they won\'t."', '"Hope,Romantic,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"It occurred to me that there was no difference between men, in intelligence or race, so profound as the difference between the sick and the well."', '"Men,Intelligence,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Action is character.', '"Character,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"No grand idea was ever born in a conference, but a lot of foolish ideas have died there."', '"Ideas,Born,Conference"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Everybody\'s youth is a dream, a form of chemical madness."', '"Youth,Madness,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'All good writing is swimming under water and holding your breath.', '"Good,Water,Swimming"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"What\'ll we do with ourselves this afternoon? And the day after that, and the next thirty years?"', '"Day,Afternoon,Next"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'At eighteen our convictions are hills from which we look; at forty-five they are caves in which we hide.', '"Look,Hide,Convictions"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Forgotten is forgiven.', '"Forgiveness,Forgotten,Forgiven"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Cut out all these exclamation points. An exclamation point is like laughing at your own joke.', '"Own,Your,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Though the Jazz Age continued it became less and less an affair of youth. The sequel was like a children\'s party taken over by the elders.', '"Age,Youth,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Advertising is a racket, like the movies and the brokerage business. You cannot be honest without admitting that its constructive contribution to humanity is exactly minus zero."', '"Business,Movies,Humanity"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'A great social success is a pretty girl who plays her cards as carefully as if she were plain.', '"Success,Great,Pretty Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"I\'ve been drunk for about a week now, and I thought it might sober me up to sit in a library."', '"Me,Drunk,Sober"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Men get to be a mixture of the charming mannerisms of the women they have known.', '"Women,Men,Charming"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'It is in the thirties that we want friends. In the forties we know they won\'t save us any more than love did.', '"Love,Know,More"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Either you think, or else others have to think for you and take power from you, pervert and discipline your natural tastes, civilize and sterilize you."', '"Power,Discipline,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Nothing is as obnoxious as other people\'s luck.', '"Chance,Luck,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Switzerland is a country where very few things begin, but many things end."', '"Country,End,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'The victor belongs to the spoils.', '"Success,Spoils,Victor"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'His was a great sin who first invented consciousness. Let us lose it for a few hours.', '"Great,Lose,Sin"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"I like people and I like them to like me, but I wear my heart where God put it, on the inside."', '"God,Heart,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Great art is the contempt of a great man for small art.', '"Art,Great,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Trouble has no necessary connection with discouragement. Discouragement has a germ of its own, as different from trouble as arthritis is different from a stiff joint."', '"Connection,Own,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'No such thing as a man willing to be honest - that would be like a blind man willing to see.', '"Man,See,Blind"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"My idea is always to reach my generation. The wise writer writes for the youth of his own generation, the critics of the next, and the schoolmasters of ever afterward."', '"Youth,Wise,Generation"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Speech is an arrangement of notes that will never be played again.', '"Will,Never,Speech"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'A big man has no time really to do anything but just sit and be big.', '"Time,Man,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"To write it, it took three months; to conceive it three minutes; to collect the data in it all my life."', '"Life,My Life,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"It\'s not a slam at you when people are rude, it\'s a slam at the people they\'ve met before."', '"People,Rude,Before"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"When people are taken out of their depths they lose their heads, no matter how charming a bluff they may put up."', '"Lose,People,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Every one suspects himself of at least one of the cardinal virtues.', '"Virtues,Himself,Every"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"After all, life hasn\'t much to offer except youth, and I suppose for older people, the love of youth in others."', '"Life,Love,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"An author ought to write for the youth of his own generation, the critics of the next, and the schoolmaster of ever afterwards."', '"Youth,Generation,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'The faces of most American women over thirty are relief maps of petulant and bewildered unhappiness.', '"Women,American,Relief"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'The compensation of a very early success is a conviction that life is a romantic matter. In the best sense one stays young.', '"Life,Success,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Her body calculated to a millimeter to suggest a bud yet guarantee a flower.', '"Flower,Body,Her"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Often people display a curious respect for a man drunk, rather like the respect of simple races for the insane... There is something awe-inspiring in one who has lost all inhibitions."', '"Respect,Man,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"The idea that to make a man work you\'ve got to hold gold in front of his eyes is a growth, not an axiom. We\'ve done that for so long that we\'ve forgotten there\'s any other way."', '"Work,Eyes,Growth"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('387999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Genius goes around the world in its youth incessantly apologizing for having large feet. What wonder that later in life it should be inclined to raise those feet too swiftly to fools and bores.', '"Life,Youth,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'For awhile after you quit Keats all other poetry seems to be only whistling or humming.', '"Poetry,Quit,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'You can stroke people with words.', '"Words,People,Stroke"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Only remember west of the Mississippi it\'s a little more look, see, act. A little less rationalize, comment, talk."', '"Look,Remember,See"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Riches have never fascinated me, unless combined with the greatest charm or distinction."', '"Me,Never,Charm"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'No decent career was ever founded on a public.', '"Decent,Career,Public"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"To a profound pessimist about life, being in danger is not depressing."', '"Life,Pessimist,Danger"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"Some men have a necessity to be mean, as if they were exercising a faculty which they had to partially neglect since early childhood."', '"Men,Childhood,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"The easiest way to get a reputation is to go outside the fold, shout around for a few years as a violent atheist or a dangerous radical, and then crawl back to the shelter."', '"Way,Back,Atheist"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', 'Scratch a Yale man with both hands and you\'ll be lucky to find a coast-guard. Usually you find nothing at all.', '"Man,Nothing,Hands"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcac', '"The world, as a rule, does not live on beaches and in country clubs."', '"World,Country,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"When I wake up every morning, I thank God for the new day."', '"God,Morning,New Day"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The influence of teachers extends beyond the classroom, well into the future. It is they who shape and enrich the minds of the young, who touch their hearts and souls. It is they who shape a nation\'s future."', '"Future,Influence,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"We are shallow because our media are so horribly shallow. Every morning, I peruse the papers, and there is so little to read in them. It is the same with radio - all that noise, that artifice."', '"Morning,Media,Radio"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"We are shallow because we have become enslaved by gross materialism, the glitter of gold and its equivalents, for which reason we think that only the material goods of this earth can satisfy us and we must therefore grab as much as can while we are able."', '"Gold,Earth,Glitter"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The heart of the theater is the play itself, how it dramatizes life to make it meaningful entertainment. To achieve depth and universality, the playwright must subject himself to intense critique, to know human character and behavior, and finally to construct art from the most mundane of human experience."', '"Life,Experience,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Poetry, fiction as novels or short stories - these are autonomous as created by their authors. They should stand on their own, like pieces of furniture that should be judged as to their usefulness, elegance."', '"Poetry,Stand,Furniture"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"We recognize the distinctness of Asian art when we turn to its traditional forms, recognize it as Japanese, Chinese and Indian, even Balinese or Thai."', '"Art,Turn,Indian"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Poetry is emotion, passion, love, grief - everything that is human. It is not for zombies by zombies."', '"Love,Poetry,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Language as a communication tool is the primary element from which literature is created. Even in pre-literate societies, it exists as songs, riddles, or epics that are chanted."', '"Communication,Language,Literature"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Colonialism subdues in many dulcet guises. It conquered under the pretext of spreading Christianity, civilization, law and order, to make the world safe for democracy."', '"Democracy,World,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Indeed, the existence of class, of social hierarchy, is as old as man himself. It prevails in the jungle where strength determines hierarchy; among men, it has also been savagely the same, whereby rulers vested with power through personal combat, or through lineal heritage as in the case of royalty, ravage their subjects."', '"Strength,Men,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Art, whatever form it takes, requires hard work, craftsmanship and creativity. As a writer, I know my grammar, cadence, the music of prose, and the art of the narrative."', '"Work,Art,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"We are shallow because we are \'mayabang,\' ego driven, and do not have the humility to understand that we are only human, much too human to mistake knowledge for wisdom."', '"Wisdom,Knowledge,Humility"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I have always admired teachers because teaching, like the priesthood, medicine and writing, is a vocation. You don\'t become a teacher because you want wealth. It is the same with writing."', '"Teacher,Wealth,Medicine"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"November is auspicious in so many parts of the country: the rice harvest is already in, the weather starts to cool, and the festive glow which precedes Christmas has began to brighten the landscape."', '"Cool,Christmas,Weather"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Past middle age, some friends suggested that I should have my eyebags removed, the deepening creases on my face stretched. I often examined my face in the mirror, imagining how I\'d look if I followed the suggestion. I decided to retain the old mug. I was too familiar and comfortable with it. And the final hindrance: the cost."', '"Age,Mirror,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Japan is very cosmopolitan - it values its origins, but a world view hovers above this narrow perspective. The interest of the Japanese in their folk culture is transcendental."', '"Culture,View,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Cultural values are, in themselves, neutral as well as universal, and so much depends on how individuals or ethnic groups use them. Values are influenced by so many factors such as geography, climate, religion, the economy and technology."', '"Technology,Religion,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"All dictators, the rich and famous, to the lowest security guard who holds a gun, easily forget that power is transitory."', '"Power,Famous,Gun"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Tourists as well as natives want to see cultural achievements - whether it\'s the Banaue Terraces, the old churches or museums."', '"See,Old,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"In a much larger sense, the problem of Sabah is directly influenced by the duplicity of imperial Britain. For whatever devious reason, the dismantling of the British empire created divisions and violence due to ethnic and religious differences."', '"Differences,Violence,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Industrialization starts with the formation of capital - it does not matter how. It can be created by saving, by the state enforcing its will on the people, by the very rich themselves."', '"Rich,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Contemplation is a luxury of the middle class, the very rich."', '"Rich,Middle Class,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'Always remember: the alleviation of poverty is never a political or economic issue - it is moral.', '"Political,Remember,Poverty"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Of course, we are all egoists. Egoism is so much a part of our humanity."', '"Humanity,Egoism,Course"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'Writing is a solitary profession; you are really alone when you write. Then the emotions become well shaped and distinct. But their transition into words must be done deliberately and with rigid artistry.', '"Alone,Emotions,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Ninoy Aquino was a friend; I knew his faults, which were outweighed by his virtues."', '"Virtues,Friend,Faults"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Writers are historians, too. It is in literature that the greater truths about a people and their past are found."', '"Past,People,Literature"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The past could liberate or imprison - it creates a nation\'s character, provides the nourishment or the poison a people imbibe in their very marrow."', '"Character,Past,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Self-respect, the value of \'face,\' is universal but is most pronounced in China, then in Japan where the Confucian ethic is most influential."', '"Face,Value,Self-Respect"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The literary depiction of life and its moral dilemmas compel us to use our conscience, to make those infallible distinctions between right and wrong."', '"Life,Wrong,Conscience"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"We must know our own roles. We should also know the roles that others play, and the rules such roles follow. In this manner, social harmony is maintained. It is when we overstep our roles, or act without knowing them, that social anarchy ensues."', '"Harmony,Rules,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Class - or the economic status of individuals - is evident in all societies, some very well stratified by a rigid caste system determined by birth."', '"Caste,Birth,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"In the visual arts, particularly painting, I distrust all those abstractions, those artificial constructions. I have a very simple way of judging them: if I can do them, they are not art."', '"Art,Simple,Painting"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I can imagine the writers of China, England and France, crippled and unsure of themselves when they feel that the ghosts of Confucius, Mencius, Chaucer and Shakespeare and Victor Hugo are looking over their shoulders."', '"Looking,Feel,Ghosts"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"For decades, as literary editor, I have followed the growth of our creative writing in English. In my Solidaridad Bookshop, half of my stock consists of Filipino books written in English and in the native languages."', '"Growth,Filipino,Half"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"You can\'t have integrity for breakfast, but try and keep it because it is perhaps the single most important word that defines not just writers but all human beings."', '"Breakfast,Integrity,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"In the Western tradition, the first writers were teachers and historians, vastly traveled, who spiced their reports with fantasies. They were also poets who sang and entertained prince and pauper."', '"Tradition,Teachers,First"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'My reading of philosophy and history is desultory; I know so much and yet so little.', '"History,Know,Reading"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I find it always pleasurable talking with young people, particularly those aspiring to be writers, out of nostalgia, and because I\'ve always felt that we oldies can learn so much from them and draw from them inspiration in our flagging and rickety years."', '"Nostalgia,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"You should live in a manner that should enable you to devote time to writing and contemplation. As is often said, the writer is at work even when he is simply looking out the window."', '"Work,Time,Window"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'A weak people and its equally debilitated leaders are bludgeoned by history. It maims them into the cripples that they are meant to be.', '"History,People,Meant To Be"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"This is the harsh truth about us: not only do Filipinos ignore books, literature - we do not understand how important the arts are - not just to those of us who work at it, but to the nation as a whole."', '"Work,Truth,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Our appreciation of folk art will strengthen our identities, our pride in belonging to a community. People trained in the creative use of their hands soon acquire skills, excellent craftsmanship which will be the most important measure of how well we can industrialize."', '"Art,Pride,Appreciation"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'I was a senior high school student at the Far Eastern University when the war with Japan broke out in 1941.', '"War,School,Far"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I said that if I were an industrialist or entrepreneur, I would invest in agriculture-based enterprises, for there is so much that can be done in manufacturing, in food preservation."', '"Food,Done,Manufacturing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The ethnic differences among Filipinos are very real. The paucity of arable land, for instance, explains the industry of the Ilokanos and the Cebuanos."', '"Differences,Real,Land"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"My wife and I often visit Rosales and the Ilokos as a matter of habit or whim induced by nostalgia, homesickness - whatever draws pilgrims to worshipped sanctuaries. Or, perhaps, what compels moths to seek the votive flame."', '"Wife,Habit,Nostalgia"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"All through history, a nation or a civilization\'s enduring glory is articulated by its mega constructions - the pyramids, the lofty cathedrals of the Christian world."', '"History,World,Glory"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I can\'t understand Urdu, Bahasa or Russian, but when the Pakistani Faiz, the Indonesian Rendra and the Russian Rosdentvensky declaim, I can feel the living throb of rhythm and music, the warmth and passion of their poetry, as do the hundreds, not a mere roomful, of poetry lovers in the audience."', '"Music,Poetry,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'I am for poetry that is admired by peasant and aristocrat alike.', '"Poetry,I Am,Peasant"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'I do not want to be bored listening to music that is muffled and known only to the poet himself.', '"Music,Listening,Bored"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"It was in the sugar hacienda in Negros, Panay and in Central Luzon where I saw the injustices heaped upon the sugar workers, particularly the sacadas, or seasonal workers."', '"Sugar,Workers,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"In the \'50s, I was traveling alone all over Mindanao, Basilan, all the way to Tawi-Tawi with just a camera and a notebook. I always stayed in the houses of Moros."', '"Alone,Way,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The Japanese bureaucracy is unique. It is also very powerful, although it is now the object of so much criticism. Many of Japan\'s brightest made it a pillar of strength and continuity."', '"Strength,Unique,Criticism"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"The Japanese covet important symbols - their heroic past as enshrined in Yasukuni, the Imperial family which has never been sullied by scandal."', '"Family,Past,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"What is needed in the theater, in fact for all our art forms, is a vibrant critical tradition."', '"Art,Tradition,Critical"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"To fund major cultural efforts, we must not rely alone on government and foundation patronage; if the farmer can spend for beer, he can pay for good entertainment which he can understand, which he can identify with and which will fortify his spirit."', '"Alone,Good,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"You perhaps know me as a novelist. Literature is one of the arts - in fact, the noblest of the arts. That is not my opinion; it was first expressed by the ancients. As art, literature has many similarities with the other art forms."', '"Art,Me,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I envy those Hindus and Buddhists who have in their religion philosophy and ancestor worship which build in the believer a continuity with the past, and that most important ingredient in the building of a nation - memory."', '"Religion,Past,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Professional societies are sooner or later fractured by the ego of their leaders. Everyone wants to be president, chairman, CEO; no one wants to be a mere follower."', '"Ego,Professional,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Literature - Eastern and Western - abounds with stories, myths, legends about the search for youth, for eternal life."', '"Life,Youth,Legends"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"For them who delay aging, who infuse decrepit bodies with youth and beauty - they must rejoice in the fullness of their deeds."', '"Beauty,Youth,Aging"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"As artists, we must not go down to the level of the masa; we should bring them up, intellectualize our languages, create classics out of our folk arts. We can do this if we are true to our roots and strive for excellence."', '"Excellence,True,Roots"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"In the end, religion teaches us to value truth, justice and freedom."', '"Freedom,Truth,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"From antiquity, Latin died but is still studied in seminaries and elite universities. So did Sanskrit in Asia. iI was replaced by Pali, but even Pali died, too. Linguists say the only ancient language which was resuscitated from the grave was Hebrew of Israel."', '"Language,Elite,Israel"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I write entirely in English; Tagalog chauvinists chide me for this. I feel no guilt in doing so. But I am sad that I cannot write in my native Ilokano. History demanded this; if it isn\'t English I am using now, I would most probably be writing in Spanish like Rizal, or even German or Japanese."', '"Sad,History,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Christianity doesn\'t demand that we worship our ancestors. If we don\'t remember our ancestors, then, in all likelihood, we cannot also recall the distant past."', '"Past,Remember,Ancestors"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Like so many poor Ilokanos, my grandparents left their village, for it could no longer sustain them. The Ilocos is a narrow coastal plain where, so often, the mountain drops to the sea. Land hunger had always afflicted the Ilokanos and made them migratory."', '"Village,Sea,Poor"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I was born in an Ilokano village called Cabugawan. Most of the houses in it were roofed with thatch, pan-aw, a species of wild grass."', '"Village,Grass,Wild"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', 'I tell young people who ask me about a future in writing not to go into it unless they get married to someone rich.', '"Future,Me,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"I regret that I have not written more, shouted louder, and acted out my beliefs."', '"Regret,More,Beliefs"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"What most readers do not realize is that it takes a particular genius to write funny, to satirize."', '"Funny,Genius,Realize"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"Some lucky people can be funny without half trying because they actually look funny, because acting funny is in their bones - fun as funny, not funny as crude slapstick."', '"Funny,Look,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcad', '"At 86, I can easily look back to the last eight decades. Though memory often fails me now, so many images of the past are still clearly polished, and I can yet recall not just an abiding sense of place, but the keen smells, the sensory responses to the events of that past."', '"Look,Me,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"The question that we must ask is whether we are making progress toward the goal of universal peace. Or are we caught up on a treadmill of history, turning forever on the axle of mindless aggression and self-destruction?"', '"History,Peace,Progress"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"In our quest for peace, we should constantly ask ourselves what we should do to create conditions in which peace can prosper."', '"Peace,Create,Quest"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"I played an integral part in helpings formulating that new vision... that we must abandon apartheid and accept one united South Africa with equal rights for all, with all forms of discrimination to be scrapped from the statute book."', '"Vision,Discrimination,New"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"You cannot say we are a healthy, dynamic democracy when one party wins almost two-thirds of the vote."', '"Democracy,Vote,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"Above all, we owe it to the children of the world to stop the conflicts and to create new horizons for them."', '"World,Children,New"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'I believe that first impressions are very important.', '"Believe,Important,I Believe That"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'It was an honour for me to have been able to work with Mr. Mandela in the process that led to the adoption of the interim constitution and our first democratic elections in April 1994.', '"Work,Me,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'President Mandela was not a hands-on president at any time.', '"Time,President,Hands-On"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'I have made the most profound apology in front of the Truth Commission and on other occasions about the injustices which were wrought by apartheid.', '"Truth,Apology,Profound"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'The relationship between me and President Mandela right at the beginning was not a very well-established relationship. It was based on two meetings.', '"Relationship,Me,Meetings"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"My predecessor, P. W. Botha, had an inner circle, and I did not like it. I preferred decisions to evolve out of cabinet discussions. That way, we achieved real co-ownership of our policies."', '"Way,Circle,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"For many years, I supported the concept of separate states."', '"Concept,Separate,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'What I haven\'t apologised for is the original concept of seeking to bring justice to all South Africans through the concept of nation states.', '"Justice,Nation,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"I felt a sense of fulfillment that an action plan, which I\'d laid on the table on the 2nd of February 1990, had been fulfilled, had been properly implemented within the time frame which I envisaged."', '"Time,Action,Frame"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"The ANC party from time to time comes with legislation which, if accepted and if not nullified by the constitution of court, would have the effect of undermining the constitution and eroding its values."', '"Time,Values,Constitution"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"When I talk about the end of apartheid, I prefer not to claim the honor that I have ended it."', '"Honor,End,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', 'It was fortunate in looking back for South Africa and its entire people that Mandela and I found it possible to work together even though big strains developed between us from time to time.', '"Work,Time,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"When I first met Mandela, we did not discuss anything of substance; we just felt each other out. He spent a long time expressing his admiration for the Boer generals and how ingenious they were during the Anglo-Boer war."', '"War,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcae', '"The government that came into power after the April 1994 elections was going to need a budget. It was drafted by our finance minister, Derek Keys, and he convinced them of the necessity to stay within the free-market principles that had been in force in South Africa for decades."', '"Power,Finance,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb0', '"I want to plug back into the hip-hop audience. Whether it be fans who grew up watching \'Yo!\', or people who have become familiar with the culture via the Internet."', '"Culture,Internet,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb0', '"I was bringing the whole music, hip-hop, art, break dancing and urban cultural thing to the downtown table."', '"Art,Music,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb0', 'People actually perceived me with being this cat from the Bronx because I\'m one of a handful of folks that was actually acting in \'Wild Style\'.', '"Me,Style,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb0', '"Although I grew up as a fan of the culture from the disco D.J. era as a young kid and hearing the beginnings of hip-hop, I\'m hearing it all from another borough in Brooklyn."', '"Culture,Young,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb0', 'I\'m just very pleased and thankful that there was a receptive audience of people that I was able to connect with.', '"Thankful,People,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'Gael Clichy who was at the club does a lot of meditation and he recommend it to me because I was such an all-action guy.', '"Me,Club,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'Sometimes when you stare adversity in the face you\'ve got to go back to those basic principles of football and do them right.', '"Football,Face,Adversity"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I always talk about being a team player, I think I\'m really good team player. I was a big voice in the changing room before games and nothing really changed for me."', '"Good,Me,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"The Everton fans seem to know football, seem to understand it, it seems to be in their blood and they really back the team."', '"Football,Fans,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"When I was at Villa and I was captain there and I had the opportunity to go to City, it played on my mind I wouldn\'t be as pivotal. So initially I didn\'t want to go, but a lot of things happened behind the scenes and I realised I had to go."', '"Opportunity,Mind,City"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"Every time I have played against Everton, whether it was home or away, straight away the first thing that comes to mind when you see the fans is passion."', '"Time,Home,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I never thought I\'d be playing 60 games a season for City, I knew I would be playing half of that if I was lucky. I knew at a club with that much power and resources there would always be a flood of players into the team."', '"Power,City,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I can be very emotional, so when it\'s the build-up to a game I enjoy that side of trying to help push the team and get them fired up."', '"Game,Help,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I wear my heart on my sleeve and I am known for getting a little bit emotional at times.', '"Heart,I Am,Wear"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"There\'s nothing worse in my book than going home with energy left over. I like to go home knowing I\'ve put a shift in, feeling that I\'ve pushed myself to the max."', '"Home,Myself,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I was a vocal presence in the dressing room as an 18-year-old at Leeds.', '"Room,Presence,Dressing Room"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I want everybody including myself to be working just as hard towards the same goal, and if that\'s not happening I think it\'s only right to voice that opinion instead of going into your shell and not speaking about it."', '"Myself,Opinion,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I just want everyone I am playing with to be fully switched on, really on it. You don\'t have to be the best player in the team to have an effect on the players around you."', '"Best,I Am,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I see ghosts all the time. Genuinely. I think I\'ve seen about four.', '"Time,See,Ghosts"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I\'m hungry. I don\'t like losing. I see myself as a winner.', '"Myself,Winner,Losing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I\'ve represented my country and played in the Premier League a long time so I am pretty realistic and confident in what I can bring.', '"Time,Long,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I feel like if the mentality is there then why not aim to win every game? We are not here just coast through games. We need to go into games thinking we are going to win.', '"Thinking,Game,Aim"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'When you go a goal behind the pressure drops off you and you feel like you can play more so when we go ahead we need to be switched on and that is when we need leaders on the pitch.', '"Feel,Pressure,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'It is definitely what my aim is to get everyone to do their part and take on that responsibility of being a leader - whether you are playing or on the bench or if you have not made the team.', '"Responsibility,Aim,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', 'I\'m a very traditional English guy who believes in hard work and dedication and giving it absolutely everything.', '"Work,Hard Work,Dedication"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I\'m an intense guy, I want to do more and my mind is racing at 100mph."', '"Mind,More,Racing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb1', '"I meditate and I have cut out red meat. For me it is just breathing techniques, learning to be still, to control your thought processes, it calms you down. It wasn\'t about dealing with the pressure of games - I\'ve always been all right in matches."', '"Learning,Me,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"As soon as Liverpool declared their interest in signing me, it was a simple decision to make. A club with Liverpool\'s history wants you? Come on, you just pack your bags and go. It will be an honour to wear the famous red shirt."', '"History,Famous,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I want to play for a club that fights to win the Champions League title.', '"Win,Club,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I am up to the speed of the Premier League, and that was what I was looking for."', '"I Am,Looking,Speed"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"With the Champions League, it\'s not bad staying at Monaco."', '"Bad,Champions League,Monaco"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I had the good luck to have the experience of training with fantastic football players like Cristiano Ronaldo, Ozil, Modric, and I also played for Real Madrid B. That was a fantastic experience because it was my first international experience as a football player and taught me a lot as a football player."', '"Experience,Good,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"The Premier League has a lot of intensity, a lot of physicality."', '"Premier League,Intensity,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I can play wherever the manager wants.', '"I Can,Wherever,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"It\'s a different playing style than at Monaco; there were two of us in midfield there, and here at Liverpool, there\'s three."', '"Style,Three,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'It is good to have someone who can help with day-to-day life for me and for my family. This is very important.', '"Life,Family,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Liverpool are known for this \'rock and roll\' football. I think I\'ve adapted well to this even if, as a player, I like to hold onto the ball longer."', '"Football,Rock And Roll,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"If the fans are liking what I\'ve been doing, and they want to create a song for me, let\'s get on with it!"', '"Me,Song,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"When I went to Real Madrid, I was only 18 or 19 years old. It was my first year as a professional footballer. I was very young."', '"Real,Young,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"It\'s good to have someone who speaks your language in everyday life, especially for me, who does not speak English so well."', '"Life,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'My process to adapt to English football has been very good.', '"Good,Football,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Guardiola, Zidane, who\'s doing a great work, Tite, also doing a great job in the national team, Simeone. These are managers I would like to work with some day."', '"Work,Great,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'There\'s no doubt about it: I think that my versatility helps me.', '"Me,Doubt,Versatility"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I get a lot of front ball in a position that, normally, the opponent\'s defense is making the move outwards, and our attackers are getting in."', '"Position,Ball,Defense"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I\'m happy at Liverpool. There\'s no reason for me to leave.', '"Me,Happy,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Firmino is a player who is really good at adapting to different positions. He is a No. 9, but he helps a lot in build-up play."', '"Good,Play,He"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Playing for relegation and livelihoods and people\'s jobs - that\'s pressure. Being at the top of the table, we should be enjoying it."', '"Pressure,People,Table"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I\'ve been fortunate enough to win titles; I\'ve been unfortunate enough to get relegated as well.', '"Win,Enough,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I haven\'t played a lot as a centre-back, but in those games, I feel like I did well."', '"Feel,Well,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'It\'s not easy to replace the best centre-back in the world.', '"Best,World,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Enjoy the games, and go on the pitch with happiness, and go game by game."', '"Happiness,Game,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I play with a lot of intensity, and I\'m quite strong in man-marking."', '"Strong,Play,Quite"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I believe I am a player that can organise the game well for my team.', '"Believe,Game,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Before signing with Liverpool, I talked to Roberto Firmino about what the club is like and what the city is like. He spoke well of the club and the city and other people who have already visited the city. The information only gave me more motivation to come to Liverpool."', '"Me,City,Information"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Sadio Mane is an excellent player. Before I came to Liverpool, I saw him on TV, and I liked him a lot."', '"Liverpool,Before,Saw"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I\'m on the right track to completely adapting to England.', '"Right,Track,Right Track"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Bernardo Silva is a key player, like Thomas Lemar."', '"Key,Like,Thomas"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I\'ve got a good understanding with Tiemoue Bakayoko.', '"Good,Understanding,Got"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"The Premier League, if not the best league in the world, is among the two best. It has a much higher visibility than Ligue 1 in France."', '"Best,World,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I was never close to signing for Manchester United, no."', '"Never,Close,Manchester United"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I was sad to leave Monaco, a club that gave me a lot of great moments, but in football, sometimes you need new challenges, and I thought it was time to move on."', '"Sad,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'Monaco have been very important for me. It\'s the club that has helped me into the Selecao.', '"Me,Important,Club"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'The Premier League is a league that I\'ve always wanted to play in. The pace is high.', '"Always,High,Pace"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', 'I have adapted well in Liverpool.', '"Well,Liverpool,Adapted"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Playing for Liverpool, I know what the relationship between the fans and the club is like. With every player, you can see the desire to win, the desire to show that Liverpool are the best and deserve to win the league."', '"Best,Relationship,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"Being in midfield, in general, you don\'t have a lot of time to think, and in the Premier League, that\'s even less of the case. You just don\'t have time to think."', '"Time,Think,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb2', '"I know it is really hard to win a league, especially the Premier League, but we have experienced players here at Liverpool."', '"Win,Know,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Going to Dubai represents a different way of life.', '"Life,Dubai,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"As a defender, you can be many shapes and sizes. You can be short and fast. Or you can be tall and jump high. It doesn\'t matter. The only necessity is that you are confident when you take the pitch - because every week there is a new challenge."', '"New,Fast,Jump"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I have thought about moving to Dubai for a while. It\'s a city that I love.', '"Love,City,Dubai"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"For me, my passion is just to play the game, it doesn\'t matter if no one comes to the stadium to watch."', '"Passion,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I didn\'t start out wanting to be a defender. Who would want to be in the back-line after having watched striker Paolo Rossi score six goals in the 1982 World Cup?', '"World,Goals,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Juventus in Italy are like Real Madrid in Spain, when you enter the team it feels different."', '"Real,Like,Real Madrid"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"In my career, Diego Maradona had the biggest influence on me."', '"Me,Influence,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'You always have to dream big and think big.', '"Big,Always,Think Big"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Del Piero is like Raul in Spain, he is the number one."', '"He,Like,Spain"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'The arrival of Beckham at Milan is not just a matter of marketing.', '"Matter,Just,Milan"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I would love to become the national team coach. I am aware that it is a tough job, but I spent 15 years with Italy. In my opinion, I have the right experience for this role and I know the environment very well too."', '"Love,Experience,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Someone who signs a contract must respect it.', '"Respect,Someone,Contract"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"My parents every day said, \'Ah, it\'s better you go to school, it\'s very important for your future.\' But inside myself, I said: \'I think the good way is follow the football.\'"', '"Future,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I\'m very proud because, all my life, I worked very hard to be a football player."', '"Life,Football,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"When you win the World Cup, you start to become a legend - for the people around the world, you are different."', '"World,Legend,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Italy is a great country, one of the most beautiful in the world, but I\'ve always gone my own way."', '"Great,Most Beautiful,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Maradona, I think, is not a football player but he\'s something different. He was unbelievable."', '"Football,Something,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Frank de Boer definitely showed in the Netherlands that he\'s a good coach.', '"Good,He,Netherlands"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I played Zidane throughout my career, and for many players you reach a point where you learn lessons on how to handle them. But from the first match I played against him to the last, Zidane would find different ways to beat me."', '"Me,Find,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I have no regrets. I won with the most prestigious clubs in the world - Real Madrid and Juventus - and also with the national team. I won the Ballon d\'Or and Fifa World Player at 33 years old.', '"World,Real,No Regrets"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"When I first arrived at Napoli, I was the ball boy, which meant that I got to watch as the legends trained. Then, once I joined the youth team as a young teenager, I was a midfielder just like Tardelli."', '"Youth,Legends,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Sure, it is true that none of us is Superman. But when we stand together, we can achieve anything."', '"Together,True,Stand"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I never saw Pele, but I watched Maradona, for seven years I saw every game. He\'s not one of the best, he\'s the best."', '"Best,Game,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I can still remember watching Italy win the 1982 World Cup. I was just an eight-year-old kid in Naples, my hometown, watching the games with a bunch of people in the houses of relatives and friends. I can recall that when Italy scored, we would shout and hug, even though we did not all know each other."', '"World,Hometown,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Zidane was the most unpleasant among my colleagues. I have never liked him on the pitch and we have always clashed. Albeit a champion for his class, I have never managed to see his fair play."', '"Colleagues,Champion,See"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"When someone becomes a part of the Azzurri squad that has won a World Cup, they are like family, and they never abandon anyone."', '"Family,World,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Ancelotti is a coach with a lot of experience. He won the Champions League while at Milan, playing some great football in the process."', '"Experience,Great,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"If the opportunity came to manage Al Ahli then why not? I would also like to one day coach one of the globe\'s great teams such as Italy, Real Madrid or Juventus."', '"Great,Opportunity,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"When the national team plays, everyone feels a part of it. Everyone comes together. And when Italians come together, we tend to do well."', '"Together,Everyone,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Of course, we all know Italy is an amazing country. We have stunning coastlines and a scenic countryside. We have a climate that allows us to spend a lot of time outdoors. We have fashion, we have food. But life in Italy is so good that sometimes we tend to rest on our laurels."', '"Life,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I watch every game in the Premier League and I like the ambience and culture of football in England.', '"Football,Culture,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I like the Klopp mentality but at the same time, I like the Pep culture about football because always we need intensity with and without the ball."', '"Time,Football,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'If you have Messi or Ronaldo you start the game 1-0 up.', '"Game,Start,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Messi is top but Maradona is another world.', '"World,Top,Messi"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I consider Zidane to be an amazing player who has written football history.', '"History,Amazing,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Juve have allowed me to show my worth, it has provided me with a challenge that has motivated me."', '"Me,Challenge,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I\'ve always been strong physically and I think for a player what happens off the field is even more important.', '"Important,Always,More"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I don\'t drink or smoke.', '"Smoke,Drink"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I respect Messi a lot.', '"Respect,Messi,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'A compact defense has always been the basis of Italy\'s team.', '"Always,Defense,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'An experience abroad really enriches you.', '"Experience,Abroad,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Of course I wish to achieve the same results as Marcello Lippi did in his career.', '"Wish,Achieve,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'You know I was a ball boy at the Italy v. Argentina semi-final in Naples in 1990 and playing in a World Cup final is something every child dreams about.', '"Dreams,World,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Football is everything for me in my life.', '"Life,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I\'m Italian and the privilege of working in my home country would fill me with pride. However, the opportunity to work in a variety of countries, learning new cultures and footballing mentalities, is also very valuable."', '"Work,Home,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"If you want to improve the football, of course you need to put attention on the academy, on the school, the facility."', '"Football,School,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Of course when you are starting to be a coach you want to do your best and my national team is my dream.', '"Best,Do Your Best,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Prandelli is a coach with great experience and he knows how to work with young people also.', '"Work,Experience,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"If you work in a certain manner, you don\'t make mistakes."', '"Work,Mistakes,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Cassano? His talent has never been in question, but his character has. As Italian captain and a big admirer I can only wish him to control his nerves better."', '"Character,Talent,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Beyond studying, though, I think a coach should mainly have knowledge of football: if you do not know what to say to the players then you are not going anywhere."', '"Knowledge,Football,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Sure it\'s a dream to coach Napoli as well as the national team.', '"Well,Dream,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I started playing football in the streets.', '"Football,Playing,Streets"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I love Forlan. He runs a lot, shoots with both feet, puts pressure on and he is intelligent and fast."', '"Love,Feet,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"You know, when you are the Italian national team, all the time you need to win because for our history, it is important for us to try to win the World Cup."', '"History,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Iniesta deserved to win the Ballon d\'Or. To win it, you have to be lucky that the attackers have not done so well. If Messi and Ronaldo score 50 or 60 goals, they will always give it to them."', '"Goals,Win,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"A coach needs time to get to know the players, the environment, the fans and the culture of the club. You can\'t solve everything in one or two months."', '"Time,Culture,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Personally, I like Jerome Boateng. He is physically strong."', '"Strong,He,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I have great respect for Juve, whom gave me so much, where I won two championships."', '"Respect,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I am Neapolitan and Naples are the team from where I grew up.', '"I Am,Up,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I have always been a Napoli fan, but the choice to move to Dubai is the right one."', '"Dubai,Choice,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I do feel I\'m a player who has played well in 2006.', '"Feel,Well,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Real are the type of club where you are expected to win every game. For a player who wants to be the best it is stimulating to feel the pressure to defend their interests.', '"Best,Game,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I think to reach a Champions League final isn\'t easy, whether it\'s in Europe or Asia."', '"Easy,Europe,Reach"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I\'m not saying there\'s no pressure at Evergrande, there\'s pressure at Evergrande all the time. But I am myself and, no matter if I\'m playing for Real Madrid or at the World Cup, I\'ve never felt pressure."', '"Time,Myself,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Being in a football environment is where I\'m most comfortable. I only feel excited and motivated when it comes to crucial, difficult, important matches."', '"Football,Difficult,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I\'m a coach who admires attacking football. I want my teams to look to win.', '"Football,Look,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"As manager of Tianjin Quanjian every day, every week, I have to give our players everything I have."', '"Day,Every Day,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I have played plenty of matches where I thought I had left everything on the field and given a game my all, but what I have come to realise since I retired and began coaching - 90 minutes on the field do not compare to life as a manager."', '"Life,Game,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"It can be lonely as a manager out there. You are on the field, yes, but you are not really on the field with them. Yet I have to share with my players my experiences and my knowledge."', '"Knowledge,Players,Field"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I began searching for my confidence on the pitch as a young boy.', '"Confidence,Young,Boy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Big or short, for me what was important was to win the game with my team."', '"Me,Game,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I was strong inside my head.', '"Inside,Strong,Head"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Size has never been a problem for me.', '"Me,Never,Size"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'It\'s always good to win in the pre-season.', '"Good,Win,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Conte is a good friend and is very charismatic.', '"Good,Friend,Charismatic"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I would recommend all players go to Napoli, it is a gratifying and successful place."', '"Place,Go,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Napoli will always have my heart, and it is normal that I want them to win."', '"Heart,Win,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I like Mourinho a lot. He has a good relationship with fans, and he always takes responsibility for his players."', '"Relationship,Good,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'Real Madrid? I don\'t have any nostalgia or bitterness.', '"Nostalgia,Real,Bitterness"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'The most imortant thing is to win.', '"Win,Most,Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"With Benitez, he should not be measured on his time at Inter. The Spanish coach has important experience. He has won trophies in England and Spain."', '"Experience,Time,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"My dream was to become the flagship player for Napoli. Even though I played for other teams, I would have liked to have returned and retired there. Napoli is my life, my city, I have regrets."', '"Life,City,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'As a player it was always not easy to play against Australia. It was always very difficult.', '"Difficult,Always,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"We often talk about this VAR, this new technology. It\'s very important new technology. On the pitch maybe it\'s not clear. You cannot see... maybe from another angle in front of the TV it\'s much more clear. But it\'s, as always, football. It\'s easy to be much more polemic about this and that."', '"Technology,Football,New"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'The only regret I can have is that Inter sold a player that is now completely recovered. I said many times that I wouldn\'t have left Inter without showing who I was. But then they sold me.', '"Regret,Me,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Obviously I want to win something important, this game is important to me."', '"Me,Game,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I\'m definitely not a perfect coach and it\'s impossible to make everyone satisfied.', '"Impossible,Perfect,Satisfied"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"For a team of Evergrande\'s level, fans hope to have the top coaches and the coach will definitely face various pressures."', '"Hope,Face,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I like Mourinho because he is intelligent. When his team are in difficulty he\'s very good at focussing the attention on himself.', '"Good,Attention,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"After winning the World Cup and the European Footballer of the Year award too, I do not think I can ask for anything else."', '"World,Award,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I had good times with Juventus but when you are offered the chance to come to Real at almost 33 years of age it is a great opportunity.', '"Good,Age,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'It\'s not one person that changes the team.', '"Person,Team,Changes"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'People who know me would know that I take one battle at a time.', '"Time,Me,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'I know that people in Guangzhou have been very kind to me.', '"Me,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'The national team has always lent its image to help Italy\'s problems over the years... The national team is more about uniting than dividing.', '"Problems,Help,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Change does not mean you will win with a new coach and achieve victories, but rather it causes instability in the team as the new coach needs some time for the players to adapt his new plans, which are always different than the previous coach."', '"Change,Time,New"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', 'My ambition with Al Ahli is to be an example for the local players. They must learn that professionalism is the path to success.', '"Success,Path,Ambition"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"I was trained under very famous coaches in the Italian national team, Read Madrid, Juventus, Internazionale and Parma."', '"Famous,Team,National"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb3', '"Now, all the people who spoke before, when I won the Golden Ball, have shut their mouths now the coaches and players from national teams have given me this prize and this recognition."', '"Me,People,Golden"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"In Italy, it is all about tactics and playing for a result, whereas in Spain, the focus is on technique and pace. In England, the game is based on aggression and non-stop action."', '"Focus,Game,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I like classy women: Virna Lisi, Catherine Deneuve."', '"Women,Classy,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"Here the football is more physically strong. The Spanish are more technical. In Italy more tactical. In England... you have to run. We don\'t fear the tackles, because the people like this."', '"Fear,Football,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I always play to win, as I proved at AC Milan, Real Madrid, Roma and Juventus. I want my players to have the same ambition."', '"Ambition,Win,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"The goalkeeper is very, very important, as much as a striker. Anyone who wants to win a title has to have a goalkeeper."', '"Win,Important,Goalkeeper"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I am not interested in the Italian national team. I prefer to have a new experience, outside of Italy."', '"Experience,I Am,New"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"When a man crosses his legs and the trouser leg rides up to show the hairy shins, it offends my eyes."', '"Eyes,Man,Legs"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"Look, in my life, I played one World Cup: the greatest thing. I used to wait in anticipation for the squad announcement. I didn\'t go to Argentina 78 having played throughout qualification. Now, that hurt."', '"Life,Look,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"Being at a World Cup is a sacrifice? Twenty days is a sacrifice? What about the people there working for the team, up at five every morning? That\'s sacrifice. It\'s not a sacrifice to play."', '"Morning,Sacrifice,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'Goalscoring depends on how relaxed you are in front of goal.', '"Depends,Front,Goal"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"At home we never mention football. Not with my wife, not with my sons, not with my mother. Sometimes they will see something in the paper and ask me what I think. But I say, nothing."', '"Home,Football,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"Having the team with leaders - John Terry is one, Gareth Barry is a leader - is very, very important. These players helped me a lot."', '"Me,Important,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'The challenge of coaching a national side like England would be something different. The job is not about coaching every day.', '"Day,Every Day,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I have always been in love with football. As a child, I started playing football."', '"Love,Football,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'The first World Cup I followed was Sweden 1958. I watched the games on TV. Brazil won that World Cup by defeating Sweden 5-2 in the Final and Pele scored twice.', '"World,Brazil,Twice"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"To train a national team, you have to know what team you have at your disposal and what this team is capable of. You need to get the best out of them and take them as far as possible. Yet, sometimes, you can\'t achieve your goals."', '"Best,Goals,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"A team needs leaders to drive it forward, but you never know how it will end."', '"Drive,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'Hotels make me sad. I need a home.', '"Sad,Home,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"When I am at work, there is no need for me to deliver anything but results."', '"Work,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I only ever call up the best players, or at least the players who are the most suited to the way I wish to play."', '"Best,Way,Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', '"I will never close the door to the national team on anyone, but you also have to remember that in modern football, only players who are in peak physical condition can make the most of their technical abilities."', '"Football,Remember,Door"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'I never had any problems with the players. I would say that my English is better than Gary Lineker\'s Spanish.', '"Problems,Better,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'My English might not be good enough to talk politics but there is no difficulty if we are talking about football.', '"Politics,Good,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb4', 'Every national side plays according to their characteristics and the kind of entertainment they like.', '"Entertainment,Side,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Life is like a Lamborghini. A Lamborghini has an engine, a body, and wheels. No matter how strong your engine is, if you don\'t have any wheels, you\'re not going anywhere."', '"Life,Body,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I speak four languages and read a great deal, so I do as much working out on the brain as I do on the body."', '"Great,Brain,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"The way I see life, there is only one God, and all the rest are human."', '"Life,God,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"A lot of people, they think, \'Oh, I\'m only going to be happy when I find a special person who is going to make me happy.\' No. In life, you have to be happy with yourself first, number one."', '"Life,Me,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"It\'s all about the whey protein and multi-mineral complexes I consume - it\'s good for my hair, and it\'s good for my skin."', '"Good,Skin,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I grew up in Milan during the golden age of designers. There was fashion all around.', '"Age,Golden,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Since I lost my sister, I decided to enjoy my life, no matter what."', '"Life,My Life,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Your mind is very powerful, and your soul knows what\'s best for you. So the more in contact you are with your soul, the more you know your path."', '"Best,Path,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"God gave you a mind, a spirit, and a body, and you should take care of all three."', '"God,Mind,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'True love is forever.', '"Love,True Love,Love Is"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"To me, the future of TV and movies is going to be 3-D animation."', '"Future,Movies,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Kim Kardashian is trash.', '"Trash,Kim,Kim Kardashian"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'You don\'t become a real man until you\'re 35 or 40.', '"Man,Real Man,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I try to limit myself to one hour of sun each day.', '"Myself,Day,Sun"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Donald Trump speaks his mind. If you like it or you don\'t like it, at least you know where he stands."', '"Mind,Know,He"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Life is short, and you have to have fun with it, you know?"', '"Life,Life Is Short,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"They don\'t call it the Italian Dream or the English Dream. In America, there is the American Dream. It was the first place to give people of any social background their dream. You can achieve anything."', '"America,People,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When you\'re happy with yourself, you have to find another person who is happy with herself so you can share your happiness."', '"Happiness,Yourself,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'There\'s not enough money in this world to make me do something degrading.', '"Money,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Everybody comes here because of the American Dream.', '"American Dream,American,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Money, power, is beautiful if you take just as fun. OK? If you don\'t get attached."', '"Money,Power,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I have all the things I can desire in life, but if I don\'t have love from people, and if I don\'t be able to give love to people and receive love, I will not be happy, even with all my success and all the money I make."', '"Life,Love,Success"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I\'m trying to tell men, \'Really show yourself. Do not be macho, because the biggest turnoff for a woman is a macho guy because women, they\'re very sensitive. They know you\'re macho because you\'re insecure.\'"', '"Women,Men,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Woman is very much more in contact with their feeling than a man. As a matter of fact, woman always teach to men how to love."', '"Love,Men,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I\'m a people person.', '"People,Person,People Person"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'The United States is the greatest country on Earth.', '"Country,Earth,Greatest"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"If you want to come to this country, the American people are the greatest people on earth and will welcome you with open arms."', '"Welcome,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I always tell people, \'I have more respect for somebody with no money and class than somebody who is trash and makes $1 billion.\'"', '"Respect,Money,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"All the Kardashians care about is the media, money, and being on camera."', '"Money,Care,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"If you want to have a balance in life, you have to have the balance of the three elements: mind, bod,y and soul. So when you reach that balance, you feel good about yourself."', '"Life,Good,Feel Good"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When you feel good about yourself, it doesn\'t matter what you\'re wearing. You are at home."', '"Good,Home,Feel Good"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I\'ve been all over the world.', '"World,Over,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'This world is always fed up with politicians.', '"World,Politicians,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'People don\'t trust anyone.', '"Trust,People,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Laws are to be respected.', '"Laws,Respected"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'California\'s a mess.', '"Mess,California"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When you believe in something, it\'s easy to promote."', '"Believe,Easy,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I see myself as a very fortunate human being.', '"Myself,See,I See"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"To me, the biggest attraction is a woman\'s charisma, her soul, her inner strength."', '"Strength,Me,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I don\'t take myself seriously, because there is so much more to life than just being good looking."', '"Life,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"That\'s a great way to work out when on the road, and it\'s fun. I love to lift women up."', '"Love,Work,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'People tend to complicate things in life.', '"Life,People,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I think the best thing is to keep your life simple.', '"Life,Best,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'There\'s nothing greener than Washington state. They have the most beautiful vegetation on the planet. And the water is so clean.', '"Most Beautiful,Beautiful,Water"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I\'m very spiritual.', '"Spiritual,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When I\'m cruising around on my bike, I feel completely free, but I share my possessions. My friends can always borrow my motorcycles. Even if they end up crashing them, it\'s OK with me."', '"Me,Free,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"A lot of people are obsessed with their possessions, but that\'s not right. It\'s OK to own a lot of things as long as you\'re willing to share them."', '"Long,People,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I\'d be the biggest hypocrite if I said I really worked very hard for my career, because it was given to me on a silver platter. I can\'t take any credit."', '"Me,Hypocrite,Credit"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Life is so fragile; you have to treasure it.', '"Life,Treasure,Fragile"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'People come to Los Angeles and sell their soul every day. It\'s sad.', '"Sad,Soul,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Miracles exist - you just have to believe it.', '"Believe,Miracles,Exist"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Ferraris always have problems. You can\'t drive them every day.', '"Drive,Day,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Lamborghini outperforms Ferrari, every time."', '"Time,Ferrari,Every"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I want to be two thousand percent sure before I get married. It should last forever.', '"Forever,Two,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"The kind of roles that Harrison Ford plays are what really interest me, like \'Indiana Jones\' and \'Raiders of the Lost Ark.\'"', '"Me,Lost,Interest"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I like to make other people feel good, and if receiving my autograph brings them a little bit of pleasure, then I\'m so glad to do it."', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I don\'t know what people expect me to be like, but I\'m very down-to-earth and not at all full of myself."', '"Myself,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When you know you\'re vulnerable, and you know... your strength and your weakness, you can see life with better perspective."', '"Life,Strength,Perspective"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Some women, they expect me to be complicated. Instead, I\'m very simple."', '"Women,Simple,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"People don\'t live a good life when they take themselves too seriously, because they\'re always concerned about what everybody else thinks."', '"Life,Good,Good Life"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I love people.', '"Love,People,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"When I was twelve, I fell in love with Candice Bergen."', '"Love,Twelve,Fell"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"As people, we have to take the law\'s side. We have to stand behind the police, not behind the criminal."', '"Police,Law,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I\'m a person, and like any person, I have feelings."', '"Feelings,Person,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I don\'t see myself as a hunk of meat.', '"Myself,See,Meat"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Since I was a little kid, everybody was paying so much attention to what I looked like, not what I was feeling. You start feeling tired. It\'s like eating soup every day. You eat the same soup, and you get bored, so I developed my inner self."', '"Tired,Day,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'The highest-quality protein in nature is whey.', '"Nature,Protein"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I like a girl with old-fashioned values - and they are very hard to find, particularly in L.A."', '"Values,Find,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"My parents always used to complain about my eating habits. I was different. I was wrong. Everything had to be plain or boiled. I was 14 before I ate pasta with tomato sauce. My dad would take me to the best restaurants, and all I would eat was rice with olive oil."', '"Best,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I cannot stand ditsy women.', '"Women,Stand,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'Your body should be treated like a Lamborghini.', '"Body,Your,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'There are few things I\'ve never done in my life.', '"Life,My Life,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I believe, in life, you always get a second chance."', '"Life,Chance,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I want to bring more lawv and romance into the society.', '"Society,More,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"If you are good to people, good will come back to you. The universe is run by this law."', '"Good,Law,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'You can\'t take yourself too seriously. You have to be secure and make fun of yourself.', '"Yourself,Fun,Seriously"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Life is a long marathon, and you have to be consistent. Anyone can sprint for 1500 meters, but you have pace yourself through your entire life."', '"Life,Yourself,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"As a kid, I was never into sweets, and I never really drank."', '"Sweets,Never,Kid"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"Always invest your money in the best food out there, and it\'s going to pay off in the long run."', '"Best,Money,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I think health is the most important thing.', '"Health,Important,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"As men, we have the illusion that we run the world."', '"Men,Illusion,World"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"You have to be a low-class scumbag to start calling a woman a name. If you\'re a man, you should never. You should be a gentleman."', '"Man,Woman,Gentleman"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"It\'s very hard for people that live in the small towns to be able to buy a certain kind of clothes because they\'re not available to them, you know. They only see them in beautiful magazines."', '"Beautiful,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I always have a love for clothes.', '"Love,Always,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"I was like, \'I would like to see everybody dress beautifully.\'"', '"Dress,See,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I love sports. I love motorcycles. Just like most guys.', '"Love,Sports,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', 'I\'m a deep person. I\'m not a superficial person at all.', '"Person,Deep,Superficial"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"To me, people are people. If a woman has a beautiful soul, and she\'s a celebrity, that\'s great. But she can be a secretary or a person working at Kmart. I don\'t care."', '"Great,Beautiful,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb5', '"One time, I took a woman on a deserted island, and we lived like Mother Nature for 10 days."', '"Nature,Time,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"If you want to aim for great targets, then you have to have a large and high-quality squad."', '"Great,Aim,Squad"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'I just focus on working hard and play with serenity.', '"Focus,Serenity,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"For Napoli\'s fans, I went from an idol to a traitor; people did not love me anymore."', '"Love,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"United are a big deal, and if it ended up going that way, I would gladly join the Premier League. It is a fascinating and beautiful competition."', '"Beautiful,Competition,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I wasn\'t a washout before, and I\'m not a phenomenon now. I\'m a player who, when he\'s called upon, is almost always there."', '"Always,Now,He"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Mancini knows what he is doing. He has to put faith in the youth; otherwise, the country will never grow."', '"Faith,Youth,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Chelsea are a very physical and technical side.', '"Side,Chelsea,Physical"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"With Conte, it was back-breaking both in training and in games."', '"Training,Both,Games"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I\'ve been lucky to have worked for many great coaches. They\'ve all been so good that maybe, at the end of my career, I\'ll give it a go myself."', '"Good,Great,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I don\'t go out there to score goals, as I am just as happy if I provide an assist for a teammate."', '"Goals,I Am,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'There\'s always competition in the national team.', '"Competition,Always,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I always say that with work and patience, if you believe in your own talent, at the end, things come back; there\'s no doubt about it."', '"Patience,Work,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'It was a dream move for me - I was at my hometown club - but I couldn\'t leave the house myself or with my family after receiving threats that suggested anything could happen at any moment. It turned my life into a nightmare. I wouldn\'t wish it on anyone.', '"Life,Family,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Napoli fans saw themselves in me. I knew I was not alone when entering the pitch, but I was there with a whole city."', '"Alone,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Just naming Batistuta gives me goosebumps!', '"Me,Goosebumps,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"A stalker tormented me for over five years. I don\'t know what was going through his mind, as he was a police officer, and because of that, I at first considered him someone to be trusted."', '"Me,Police,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"People accused me of leaving Napoli for money, but that was not true and really annoyed my family."', '"Family,Money,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Would I go back to Napoli? It\'d be wonderful even to just know those fans had thought of me. I left unfinished business there.', '"Business,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'I\'ve had to deal with terrible things being said about me.', '"Me,Things,Terrible"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I was forced to leave my hometown, and Napoli sold me to Juventus."', '"Me,Hometown,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"As a professional, I have always tried to stay concentrated on the pitch, but it was not easy."', '"Always,Professional,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Chelsea and Shakhtar are two great teams.', '"Great,Two,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Inter have some great players, and they are a team who will fight for the Scudetto, along with Napoli."', '"Great,Fight,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"This is the Italian national team; there\'s no need to give caps away. If the coach calls up certain players, it\'s because he\'s convinced they can give a big hand, and that\'s why I\'m here."', '"Big,Why,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Being called up by the Azzurri is a great source of satisfaction. There are so many strong young players with great personalities, and for me, it\'s nice to be here, even if I\'m playing it by ear."', '"Great,Me,Satisfaction"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"You cannot always play at 100 per cent, especially at the end of the season when you don\'t have much energy left."', '"Energy,End,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I love it in Udine, no doubt about it, but I am clearly pleased to read that other sides are interested in me."', '"Love,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Who wouldn\'t like to play for a big side?', '"Big,Side,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Playing at Juventus is an important step in my career. It is a very big club.', '"Step,Important,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Even though I am at Turin and think about Juve, for me, Napoli is Napoli, and it is my home."', '"Home,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Napoli wanted to send me to Rubin Kazan, and I knew nothing about it."', '"Me,Nothing,About"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'I don\'t regret leaving Napoli.', '"Regret,Leaving"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I like the Italian giants, and Spain is attractive, but when I heard that Manchester United were in the frame, I was very flattered. Nonetheless, I want to reiterate that Udinese is a great place, and I am happy here."', '"Great,I Am Happy,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'I am and always will be a Napoli fan.', '"I Am,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Everyone has the right to a peaceful life.', '"Life,Everyone,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"We are Italy. It\'s only right that there is competition in attack, like there is in every other role."', '"Competition,Attack,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Foreign players are great for Serie A if they add something extra, but a lot of them are superfluous."', '"Great,Players,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"It\'s the first hat trick of my career, so I will treasure the match ball."', '"Hat,Will,Treasure"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Wayne Rooney has always made a great impression on me, even though I have only ever seen him on television."', '"Great,Me,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"Juve\'s secret is that we always believe, up until - even beyond - the 90th minute."', '"Believe,Always,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I know my talents well - I know my head well - so when I go onto the pitch, I know perfectly what I have to do."', '"Know,Go,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'I am accustomed to making the most out of my opportunities.', '"I Am,Opportunities,Making"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', 'Juve are one of the most important clubs in the world. Who would walk away from that?', '"Walk,World,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb6', '"I was brought on and scored, so I will never forget my Champions League debut."', '"Never Forget,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"For me, my home is a peaceful place where I can rest, and it gives me back energy."', '"Home,Me,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'It\'s always good news when you\'re closer to the truth.', '"Truth,Good,News"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'There is nothing more exciting than having a life devoted to fundamental knowledge and to contributing to advance the borders of knowledge.', '"Life,Knowledge,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"We had to understand things like why the top quark was so heavy and the electron is so light. The Higgs is a big, important step."', '"Light,Step,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'Diversity is really a richness for mankind.', '"Diversity,Mankind,Richness"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"In the big experiments, Atlas and CMS, we have something like 3,000 scientists each, and over 60 nationalities."', '"Big,Experiments,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Musical harmony is based on physical principles, while in cooking, ingredients must be weighed out with precision. At the same time, you have to be able to invent because if one follows the same recipe all the time, you never create anything new."', '"Time,Cooking,Harmony"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"CERN is a concrete example of worldwide, international co-operation - and a concrete example of peace. The place which makes, in my opinion, better scientists, but also better people."', '"Peace,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"I like manual things, doing things with my hands, the feeling of touching."', '"Hands,Doing,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'Working with so many people from all over the world is extremely enriching and stimulating.', '"World,People,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Of course, mankind has made giant steps forward. However, what we know is really very, very little compared to what we still have to know."', '"Know,Forward,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Art is based on very clear, mathematical principles like proportion and harmony. At the same time, physicists need to be inventive, to have ideas, to have some fantasy."', '"Time,Art,Harmony"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"CERN is a centre of scientific excellence and a source of pride and inspiration for physicists from all over the world, a cradle for technology and innovation, and a shining concrete example of scientific cooperation and peace."', '"Peace,Technology,Pride"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'We will have to be very vigilant that young female scientists have the same opportunities as their male colleagues.', '"Colleagues,Will,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Like in nature, I like things which are based on a few simple principles, even though their manifestation can be very rich."', '"Nature,Simple,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'The search for knowledge is a long and difficult task.', '"Knowledge,Long,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"We know there must be new physics. For example, we cannot explain what dark matter is."', '"New,Dark,Physics"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"I will fully engage myself to maintain CERN\'s excellence in all its attributes, with the help of everybody, including CERN Council, staff and users from all over the world."', '"Myself,World,Excellence"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', 'The training of younger generations is very close to my heart.', '"Heart,Training,Younger"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"The top quark was discovered in 1995, and since then, the Higgs has become our obsession because the standard model was incomplete without it."', '"Obsession,Because,Top"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Among the questions we have in mind: dark matter, antimatter, and matter symmetry."', '"Mind,Dark,Questions"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"My efforts are focused on ensuring that CERN maintains a leading role in the fields of science, technology and education, and that it continues to be a place that unites scientists from around the world."', '"Education,Science,Technology"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"From a scientific point of view, our mission is to seek answers to the fundamental questions about the universe. Many are open - we don\'t know about dark matter, which accounts for a quarter of the universe\'s matter, nor do we know why there\'s antimatter."', '"View,Universe,Mission"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Our research is so complex that the resources of a single region of the world are no longer enough - both intellectually and economically, it must be a global effort."', '"World,Effort,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"Our laboratory is a place that celebrates diversity and is totally open to all differences, not just sex but also age, ethnicity, religion and other traditions."', '"Age,Religion,Sex"', '2023-05-29 11:35:00', '2023-05-29 11:35:00'),
	('388453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb7', '"With the discovery of the Higgs boson, one of the questions has been ticked off the list, but there are many others. We hope that we can find answers or hints for answers to at least some of them. But of course, this is in the hands of nature."', '"Nature,Hope,Hands"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"The thing about marriage is that I believe in it, but don\'t believe in it. I think sometimes people put that ring and that paper and it messes up a good thing."', '"Good,Marriage,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Michael Jordan broke the mold of the Magic Johnson/Larry Bird era - he came in and he had a gold chain, he wore longer shorts and his sneakers were a different style."', '"Bird,Style,Gold"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Sometimes in life, your best teacher is experience and going through something to figure it out."', '"Life,Best,Experience"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'And I would like to work with Eminem. Because I\'ve always been a fan of his work.', '"Work,Always,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I feel like I can really adapt to any type of fashion sense that I want to.', '"Feel,I Can,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Certain people have that feeling like \'I want to know this. I want to know that.\' I have none.', '"People,Know,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"When you get the light shined on you, it\'s always interesting to see how people do in that light. The light shines on you, the spotlight\'s on you, so what are you going to do?"', '"Light,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I think that\'s where the music business is where it is today because at one point, we were just splurging so much money and it was just extra. Everything was just extra and over did. Now, people are being as creative as they were but they\'re not spending $500,000 or a million on a video."', '"Business,Money,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I used to to hustle growing up.', '"Growing Up,Up,Hustle"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I never put myself at a bragging point where I say, \'I\'m gonna have the illest verse.\'"', '"Myself,Never,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I had a certain level of patience, but sometimes weathering the storm is a patient process. Every storm don\'t pass fast. Every storm, it can be passing, but it can be getting stronger and stronger or it could be coming down hard."', '"Patience,Storm,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I\'m very observant. So, my mentor is really basically a lot of people who are just around me and life itself. Just living and going different places and traveling."', '"Life,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I go from streetwear to high-end fashion, to being formal and wearing suits."', '"Fashion,Go,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Me and Pusha have always been cool even though we haven\'t done many collaborations.', '"Cool,Me,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Sometimes you have crazy ideas that sound crazy to everybody, but I\'m sure everybody has had a crazy idea before. When you pull it off and you don\'t look crazy anymore, you look like a genius."', '"Look,Crazy,Genius"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I don\'t think that marriage is in the future for me, I really don\'t."', '"Future,Marriage,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I noticed that what you\'re wearing is a representation of yourself and speaks for you before you do.', '"Yourself,Before,Representation"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"You gotta claim the crown and the people also gotta crown you, too. It\'s not just about somebody saying they king."', '"King,People,Crown"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"That\'s the kind of lane that I try to keep my fashion usually in - not too uppity, not too out of the norm, but little touches that make it special."', '"Fashion,Try,Special"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Even before I became an artist myself, I always cared about my presentation."', '"Myself,Always,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"It\'s one thing to see the clothes on a rack, but it\'s interesting to see how they get brought to life."', '"Life,See,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I think the worst thing you could do is not shoot the shot. When you shoot you got two options: It can go in or you can miss, and even in the miss you might learn."', '"Worst,Shoot,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Whether I\'ve been here three years or 10 years, my agenda is still in the same place as it was when I first came in: it\'s to continue to make good music, and raise the bar to grow and evolve as a person, as an artist, as everything; just to be a better me."', '"Good,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I just wanted to make good music that people related to me and said \'Yo that guy makes good music. When he gives us an effort, it\'s good music behind it. It\'s great lyrics, it\'s witty punchlines, it\'s great metaphors.\'"', '"Good,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I won\'t change myself and compromise myself, but I will make my music to be in the conversation with everyone else\'s."', '"Change,Music,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I like when videos used to make you sit at home, and you\'d watch it and be like in awe like, \'I wish I was at that place, man. I wanna go on a vacation.\'"', '"Home,Man,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Me and Chainz hang out, we talk. I go to Atlanta, I go to Chainz\'s restaurant. Chainz came to my dinner. Chainz is my guy."', '"Restaurant,Me,Dinner"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Jay-Z has always been a huge figure in hip-hop.', '"Hip-Hop,Always,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'The holiday time is where people slow down a little bit more. You get a chance to really take in an album.', '"Time,Chance,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Just finding the right balance of career, family, personal goals, personal feelings. All of that is part of life and part of growing up."', '"Life,Family,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I\'m more into myself with my family, and my personal life is usually handled inside, it\'s not usually public, with opinions, comments, family members involved - them reacting to everything."', '"Life,Family,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Part of leaving your legacy is not worrying what everyone is saying about it.', '"Legacy,Everyone,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I don\'t take Twitter that serious. It\'s all in good humor. I\'ve made fun of people on Twitter and it\'s whatever.', '"Good,Humor,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Its shocking to come from doing freestyles to having the No. 4 album in the country. It pushes me to do better and better so I can get to No. 1.', '"Me,Better,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Even sometimes, when you\'re at home with the family, you need a break from them, really."', '"Family,Home,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"In 20 years, a lot of things change, especially in music. From CDs to tapes to vinyl to digital now, you know, a lot changes."', '"Change,Music,Digital"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I\'m definitely a little surprised at what hip-hop was able to do to my life.', '"Life,My Life,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"It\'s not just in The Bronx or in the ghettos or even just America. It\'s worldwide. Who knows, it could be some aliens on Mars listening to hip-hop, you know what I mean? So it\'s really, really transformed from this little thing of ours to a thing for everyone."', '"America,Listening,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I think that\'s one thing that hinders hip-hop and I think when everybody tries to be the same... That\'s why people look at the 1990s almost like it was a golden era in hip-hop \'cause it was so much diversity in the music and in the artists. It wasn\'t everybody just trying to paint the same picture and say it with the same flow.', '"Music,Look,Diversity"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I had a studio session with Nipsey Hussle. We didn\'t record, but we just vibed and we talked. It was just good conversation. We played music for each other that we had previously worked on. It was a good vibe."', '"Good,Music,Conversation"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I want to work with Nas.', '"Work,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"As a celebrity, you have to have some type of peace of your personal life."', '"Life,Peace,Celebrity"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Look at Jay-Z and Beyonce. Everybody knew Jay and Beyonce were dating. They were sitting around at award shows together like they weren\'t together for a while before they came out and said whatever. But your life doesn\'t always have to be exposed. There are a lot of people whose personal lives aren\'t exposed.', '"Life,Dating,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'What you grow up listening to makes the kind of person that you are.', '"Grow,Listening,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I really respect Hov\'s drive, as well as his whole career and what he\'s done for the culture."', '"Respect,Culture,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"In music, if somebody makes a good song, you want to be in that category and make the good songs too. It may not even be a competition thing, it\'s just a thing to keep your skills up type of thing."', '"Good,Music,Competition"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I\'ve just grown as a person. I think that\'s what helped me grow as an artist.', '"Me,Grow,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I put a lot in my mixtapes, but I definitely put a lot into my albums as well."', '"Well,Definitely,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I know a lot of people like mixtape Fab, and albums, to me, you\'re speaking to a broader audience sometimes. I take that at hand."', '"Me,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Stay in school... Even being a rapper you need an education.', '"Education,School,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Some of the ways I write my raps is from my vocabulary I learned in school.', '"School,Vocabulary,Learned"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Streetwear is pretty comfortable.', '"Comfortable,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I love collaborations because I love the mixture of the minds.', '"Love,Because,Minds"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'That\'s where my fashion comes from; it comes from versatility. You can mix and manage different things.', '"Fashion,Versatility,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Sometimes you say punchlines or say things in music and you may not even know any seriousness behind it. You\'re just trying to say something in the moment to catch attention.', '"Music,Moment,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Beyonce is graceful, man. Even her way of checking you is graceful."', '"Man,Way,Graceful"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I got to go to Ghana, Africa and I got to go to the Dominican Republic. You know, just across the world and see their response to my music."', '"Music,World,See"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"A lot of rappers nowadays will say they don\'t listen to anybody, but I like to hear what\'s going on. I don\'t think it affects my music. I still do what I do. I just listen as a fan because I love hip-hop."', '"Love,Music,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I mean there\'s no other feeling than when you hear a great hip-hop song. You feel good. If you lose that as an artist, you lose a part of your passion."', '"Good,Great,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Part of the passion for me was hearing great music from the very start of it, now I\'m one of the people who can give that passion back to somebody."', '"Music,Great,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I used to be a pretty good player back in the day. But I don\'t play basketball too much anymore.', '"Good,Day,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I look at where I\'ve come from and realize that I\'m lucky to make it out. I was a mischievous kid and I understand the whole reasoning of youth today because I didn\'t have much to do in the afternoon after school.', '"Today,Youth,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Basketball has a culture to it, it has a swagger to it."', '"Culture,Basketball,Swagger"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'There\'s an art to basketball; there\'s a passion to it.', '"Art,Passion,Basketball"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I\'m working on this reality show, with me and my son. It\'s gonna be like, about young fatherhood where, well, not too young, but in the same token as being my first child and he\'s so young and me still being relevant in hip-hop. You know, having to balance my career being a father at the same time."', '"Time,Reality,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Everybody\'s out and you get a lot of friction, a lot of heat in the air. It makes a beautiful disaster and that\'s where the \'Summertime Shootout\' comes from."', '"Beautiful,Heat,Disaster"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I remember so many times in the summer there was shootouts and things going on and it was just a part of it. It wasn\'t even like you regretted it; you still was looking forward to next summer. It was like oh damn, my man got killed but we gon\' rep him and next summer we gonna ball again. It was just a part of the culture."', '"Man,Culture,Looking Forward"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I think growth is a big part of everything, it think even growth for Brooklyn, growth for Downtown Brooklyn is good."', '"Good,Growth,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"As I continue my artistry, I want to touch places that I haven\'t gone and do certain music that I haven\'t done over and over again."', '"Music,Done,Continue"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I\'m not as big of an R&B fan as people like to think, but I just love the marriage between R&B and Hip-Hop."', '"Love,Marriage,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"There\'s a song on there called \'Slow Down,\' and it\'s about a girl who could be wifey but is just moving to quick, partying; needs to slow down. A lot of ladies can relate; they might know someone or be that girl."', '"Song,Slow,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Your van can get stolen anywhere I guess.', '"Your,Guess,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'D.C. shows me a lot of love.', '"Love,Me,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I put too many years in business of me working in this industry for me to be a piece of somebody else\'s thing.', '"Business,Me,Industry"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I would be involved in a show that was something like \'Run\'s House\'... that\'s a different kind of show.', '"House,Something,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I wouldn\'t do a \'For The Love of Fabulous\' kind of show at all.', '"Love,Fabulous,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I remember one time 50 was offering me different things to come and be apart of G-Unit. I didn\'t really do it because it was kind of at the time where they were signing Mobb Deep, Ma$e and M.O.P. I didn\'t know if I wanted to be up under something."', '"Time,Me,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'People always ask me why I didn\'t join a crew or something like that. I don\'t know if that would have changed my legacy or if I would still be here today.', '"Today,Me,Legacy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"When I first came in, family life wasn\'t at the forefront of your career or who you were as an artist. You was even supposed to be projected as a single man for the public."', '"Life,Family,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I really didn\'t know DMX was married or Ja Rule was married.', '"Know,Really,Rule"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I think people know what I do - they know I\'ve been in the game for a minute, but you gotta continuously show that growth and show that you\'re bringing something."', '"Growth,Game,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"If you want something of good quality, you gotta take your time with it."', '"Time,Good,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I like fashion shows. I like the quick flash of culture and energy.', '"Culture,Energy,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I try to have a fashion sense as far as looking and being fresh in my space. I guess that gets received well sometimes but I never look at myself as a \'fashionista\' or \'style icon.\'', '"Space,Myself,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I like being different and having options.', '"Being Different,Options,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I like to try new things as well as stay in my comfort zone so I think all the styles or looks I do, represent me."', '"Me,New,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"If I was Bill Gates, I would double Bill Gates, you know what I mean? That\'s the mindstate you should keep in any profession, just keep striking iron and trying to get bigger and better."', '"Better,Know,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I\'m not just rapping because I like it anymore - this is like almost my career now, you know? Not almost, it is! This is what I feed myself and my family with, so I attack it that way."', '"Family,Myself,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'Ne-Yo is just like a writing genius.', '"Genius,Writing,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I definitely would like to embark on acting, give it a shot, you know maybe that\'s my calling, maybe it\'s not."', '"Acting,Know,Shot"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I\'m a big boxing fan.', '"Big,Boxing,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Before I was a musician, I drew. The housing projects in Brooklyn weren\'t much of a canvas, people didn\'t know that I had it in me - but I actually went to an art and design high school."', '"Art,Design,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I don\'t like the idea of pre-meditated music. Things like free-styling, the element of surprise - I think people need to scale back and re-focus on making moments again."', '"Music,Surprise,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"The Mary J. Blige song is called \'My Life.\' It\'s kinda like an autobiography song, stating what I\'m about and what I\'m trying to do and what I\'ve done."', '"Life,My Life,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I am kinda like, if I don\'t really know people I am a little passive and a little quiet, and you know most of my friends they know a different side of me, so I guess that\'s what kinda Twitter gets to see a little bit, things that I would say around my friends and joke around with."', '"Me,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Twitter, I always say is the drunk uncle of my personality, because I say some stuff sometimes that, you know that drunk uncle at the Thanksgiving table, he starts rambling on about, that he shouldn\'t have said so sometimes I do that."', '"Thanksgiving,Personality,Drunk"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"I think Twitter is great for showing your personality and just your random thoughts and dropping a jewel on your listeners, fans and followers."', '"Great,Personality,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"Me and Drake, we just met each other in passing on the road. We kicked it a few times. We kept ending up in the same circles. Eventually we figured out we wanted to work."', '"Work,Me,Ending"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', '"LeBron\'s a close friend of mine, so I always root for him."', '"Always,Mine,Friend"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb8', 'I like comfortable settings. Just somewhere where you can sit and chill and you got your friends and you got drinks and food.', '"Food,Chill,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', 'The most important impact on society and the world is the cell phone. Cell phones have actually been one of the primary drivers in productivity improvements.', '"Society,World,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"I actually think the one who is underestimated in terms of impact he\'s had on society is Bill Gates. The reason is that with the innovation of software, he really allowed the computer revolution to take hold."', '"Society,Innovation,Impact"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"As an entrepreneur you keep trying things, and I try everything. I try business ideas, on our website we test everything, iterate, iterate, iterate."', '"Business,Website,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"I could have probably been just as successful by not going to college, but it was the most intellectually stimulating environment that I was ever in."', '"Environment,Just,College"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"Learn computer science. It\'s extraordinarily helpful. I like recommending learning economics as well so they think in terms of business, they have rational frameworks for looking at the world, but yeah, computer science is an amazing way to get into, even if you want to be CEO, having a tech background is helpful."', '"Science,Business,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"If you\'re CEO of a company, you have to be a public person. You\'re speaking to the press, you\'re speaking to investors, you\'re speaking to employees, you\'re the public face of the company and so kind of naturally you become more extroverted, more outwards facing."', '"Face,Company,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"Forty percent of my portfolio is in the U.S. In the rest of the world, most of the places I invest in or invested in are Brazil, Russia, Germany with a little bit of Turkey, China, India, France and Israel sprinkled in there."', '"World,Rest,Brazil"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcb9', '"Is the button white or orange or green or yellow? Does it say \'sell\', or \'sell now\', or \'on sale\' or \'for sale\'? You test, you test, you test and most of the ideas you try fail and so I would argue I failed my way to success."', '"Success,Green,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcba', '"For me, French is so rich and so sacred that learning it is like learning a foreign language."', '"Learning,Me,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcba', 'I am a free man. I don\'t need to earn money. But I need to love what I do.', '"Love,Money,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'You don\'t appreciate life until you get to the other side. Like lying in a hospital bed.', '"Life,Hospital,Bed"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', '"Family and God - that is what\'s important. Money, cars, those are things that come and go."', '"Family,God,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'I am walking proof of the power of prayer.', '"Power,Prayer,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', '"There\'s more to life than football, right?"', '"Life,Football,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'For me there is no such word as \'luck\' in the dictionary.', '"Me,Luck,Dictionary"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'I don\'t particularly get nervous about anything.', '"Nervous,Anything,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'I\'m a very competitive person.', '"Person,Competitive,Competitive Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbb', 'I\'ve lived most people\'s dream by playing football.', '"Football,People,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Fake news is a big thing in the field of Social Media Journalism. Fake news can be as simple has spreading misinformation.or as dangerous as smearing hateful propaganda.', '"Simple,Journalism,Social Media"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"No matter how frustrated, disappointed and discouraged we may feel in the face of our failures, it\'s only temporary. And the faster you can stop wallowing in guilt, blame or resentment, the faster you can put it behind you."', '"Face,Feel,Blame"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"\'No one can make you successful; the will to success comes from within.\' I\'ve made this my motto. I\'ve internalized it to the point of understanding that the success of my actions and/or endeavors doesn\'t depend on anyone else, and that includes a possible failure."', '"Success,Failure,Motto"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The American Dream is that any man or woman, despite of his or her background, can change their circumstances and rise as high as they are willing to work."', '"Change,Work,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Raising the minimum wage represents a substantial financial burden for employers, particularly start-ups, early stage companies, and family-owned businesses. In response, business owners would be forced to either lay off workers or raise prices to offset the rise in labor costs."', '"Business,Rise,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Many people dream about being an entrepreneur, starting their own business, working for themselves, and living the good life. Very few, however, will actually take the plunge and put everything they\'ve got into being their own boss."', '"Life,Business,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Real estate investing is unique in that it\'s almost as much a career or a way of life as it is a form of investing. Indeed, the fact that real estate is involves so much sweat equity makes it unique among other investments."', '"Life,Sweat,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Business is all about the customer: what the customer wants and what they get. Generally, every customer wants a product or service that solves their problem, worth their money, and is delivered with amazing customer service."', '"Business,Money,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Brexit was not a coup. Far from it. In the eyes of most analysts, it was a clear sign that people are frustrated and fed up with the status quo; this is particularly the case with independent voters."', '"Eyes,People,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Raise the taxes, and we find less money in our pockets. Lower the taxes, and we\'ve got more money in those pockets, and we spend it on all kinds of things."', '"Money,Find,More"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Voting third-party in 2016 meant choosing The Green Party\'s Jill Stein, the Libertarian Party\'s Gary Johnson, or Independent Candidate Evan McMullion."', '"Green,Independent,Candidate"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Beware of politicians who tell you they\'ll do all these wonderful things for you for only a small tax increase. Those tax increases are never as small as you might imagine, and the benefits are always smaller than promised and/or imagined."', '"Politicians,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The business side of real estate investing is fraught with risk. Unlike purchasing mutual funds or savings bonds, with real estate, you can lose money; this is one of the reasons that seasoned real estate investors caution neophytes never to get too emotional about a property and always be willing to walk away."', '"Business,Money,Walk"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"There are signs jobs will be plentiful in the future, if we train and prepare for it. That means investing in technology, innovation, and, as much as Republicans will hate to hear this, renewable energy."', '"Future,Technology,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Immigrants use debt intelligently. They understand the difference between active debt: creating a business, or something to make business better, and dead debt: buying that new sports car or the 60 inch television. Those things don\'t lead to the good life. They delay getting it."', '"Life,Car,Business"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Starting a new business will take its toll on your time and energy, and this can place strain on family and social relationships, depending on their expectations and how open you are in your communication with them."', '"Family,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"A fascinating reaction of the human brain when we fail to meet a goal is that it tells us to throw caution to the wind and make things even worse, which ultimately leads to us giving up."', '"Brain,Wind,Human Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"When you are just starting out with an online business, there\'s a good chance that you\'ll be making several mistakes. Because of the mistakes that can be made with starting an online business, many people decide to quit or think that online businesses are just a scam."', '"Business,Good,Chance"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Carrie Underwood was just a small-town Oklahoma girl with big dreams in 2005 when she competed on the fourth season of \'American Idol.\' She is one of the few true \'American Idol\' success stories and went on to have incredible career success.', '"Dreams,Success,True"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Stock photos are used everywhere on the Net. Chances are, the website you are on right now uses stock photos somewhere - maybe as the featured image of the blog post. This also means that there will always be a large market for stock photographers."', '"Website,Will,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Relying on someone else to be successful only ties you down and limits you.', '"Limits,Someone,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"There are a whole host of psychological phenomenon humans have developed to protect ourselves from the sting of failure, from holding ourselves less accountable for our failures than we do other people, to letting our fear paralyze us and keep us from even trying."', '"Failure,Fear,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'One way to quantify the immigrant contribution to the overall economy is to measure their share of the U.S. economic output. One such examination for the years 2009-2011 found that immigrants contributed 14.7 percent of the total economic output.', '"Way,Measure,Immigrant"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Lauren Conrad has been described as one of the first people to significantly benefit from the popularity of reality TV.', '"Reality,People,First"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Microsoft, Disney, Ford, Facebook, and a hundreds and thousands of other companies that affect us daily all began life as baby companies, aka start-ups."', '"Life,Daily,Baby"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"While the Forbes Council does offer some benefits and opportunities for members, the Council may want to be careful going forward to avoid the many pitfalls that befell Trump University."', '"Avoid,Careful,University"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Although advertised as \'invite only\', it has been reported by Forbes Council members and invitees that this \'invite\' came with a membership fee."', '"Only,Membership,Invite"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Successful entrepreneurship takes complete dedication and careful strategizing along with market analysis. Plus, successful startups provide countless benefits to a healthy economy and consumers in need."', '"Dedication,Careful,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"One of the most important aspects that feed a thriving economy is successful businesses, so the more startups that take off, the better the financial picture is for everyone."', '"Better,Picture,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"On the consumer level, the products developed by entrepreneurs help to provide more and better options that make life easier and more enjoyable in the everyday lives of the public."', '"Life,Better,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Launching a successful product or startup has little to do with luck. Any business that gains traction on the market is the result of very careful strategizing and market analysis, not to mention the development of an original product or service."', '"Business,Service,Luck"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"When the government takes more money out of the pockets of middle class Americans, entrepreneurs, and businesses, it lessens the available cash flow for people to spend on goods and services, less money to start businesses, and less money for businesses to expand - i.e. creating new jobs and hiring people."', '"Money,Government,New"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Lower taxes will stimulate your own personal economy by leaving more money in your pocket to do what you want - invest, save, spend, buy a bigger house, a nicer car, and give to charity. And lower taxes also lead to more money for the government to use on those things they\'ve promised you. It\'s a win-win for everyone."', '"Car,Money,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Mr. Trump, you were elected mainly because you found a way to connect with the average blue-collar worker who\'s sick of the games politicians have been playing for years. Those same blue-collar folks, who go to church, want to feed their families, have to pay their taxes."', '"Way,Church,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Mr. Trump, Americans can\'t afford, and don\'t want, to worry about the latest lawsuit filed against their president. And you\'re not immune from these suits once you enter the Oval Office. Anything you\'ve done before taking office is fair game."', '"Game,Done,Worry"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Executive orders are meant for occasional use, not to force something through that the people\'s elected representatives aren\'t going to make law."', '"Law,People,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"America is unique in the world. If you don\'t believe that, just ask someone from another country."', '"Believe,World,America"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"When it comes to finances, immigrants are far savvier than native-born Americans. They keep their expenses low. They save their money."', '"Money,Far,Immigrants"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"False news, when combined with social media, can wreak havoc thanks to its potential of reaching millions in a short span. The effects can be quite disturbing."', '"Social Media,News,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"If you can build a Facebook page and channel the audience to your website, you can generate revenue via PPC advertisement networks like Google Adwords, Taboola, Yahoo! Bing Network, AdRoll, 7Search, etc."', '"Website,Build,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The \'Fake News Alert\' Chrome extension, created by \'New York Magazine\' journalist Brian Feldman, identifies hoax news articles. However, cutting out fake news source entirely from operating is easier said than done, since anyone with internet access can create fake news."', '"Internet,News,New"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"With Donald J. Trump\'s arrival to power, many feel astonished by the growth of populism. Others analyze with extreme care the decline of companies that measure public opinion. I am saddened to watch the lack of temperament and political stability of those who \'represent\' a trend or ideology."', '"Power,Growth,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"For members of the Democratic Party, and progressives all over the world, it is difficult to overstate or hyperbolize the despair and dread that has descended upon them in the wake of President-elect Donald Trump."', '"World,Difficult,Despair"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The truth is that for a Democrat to triumph in a presidential election, it needs to come on the heels of \'the dark times\' of an unpopular Republican administration. Carter followed the Nixon era, Clinton succeeded after 12 years of Reagan/Bush, and Obama was a direct result of eight years of Bush/Cheney."', '"Truth,Result,Election"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Kennedy was like a rock star. Carter was the earnest outsider at the height of Washington cynicism. Clinton was a bad boy who proposed his \'third way\' of Democratic politics, and Obama brought hope and change to a country that so desperately needed it."', '"Change,Politics,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"It\'s more than a little ironic that the mantra that swept Bill Clinton into office is exactly what prevented Hillary from winning it. Somehow, the Manhattan billionaire became the voice of the disaffected blue-collar middle class in states like Ohio, Pennsylvania, and Michigan."', '"Winning,Voice,Middle Class"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The very phrase \'Make America great again\' implies some kind of reset to a time long since passed. A mission to restore America to a previous default setting where American economic superiority was without peer, factories and manufacturing plants were humming, and jobs were plentiful for anyone who wanted one."', '"Time,Great,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The study titled \'Impact of Immigration on Wages, by Education Level, 1994-2007\' found that increased immigration had an effect of lowering wages for earlier immigrants by an average of 4.6 percent. Running counter to popular perception is the finding that for native-born Americans, wages actually increased by 0.6 percent."', '"Education,Perception,Impact"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"A big part of the anti-immigration narrative is the perception that the majority of immigrants are poor, uneducated, and unskilled."', '"Perception,Poor,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Cuban Americans have little in common with immigrants from Mexico and Central America, and often their priorities don\'t align. If it seems like Cuban Americans don\'t have to play by the same rules as everyone else, that\'s probably because they don\'t."', '"America,Rules,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"In 1995, the Clinton Administration reached an agreement with Cuban government that any refugee caught at sea would be sent back to Cuba while any refugee who reaches the United States shores would be allowed to begin the process to citizenship after one year."', '"Government,Process,Sea"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"If you\'re an independent voter, I\'m willing to bet that you were not too happy at the prospect of hitting the polls on November 8, 2016. But let me guess - you did it anyway because after all, it\'s your civic duty, right?"', '"Me,Duty,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"If the 2016 election is any indication, every four years, millions more Americans will continue backing away from their own parties to choose a third party instead."', '"Election,Will,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Remember, your vote is not a wasted vote. Vote with your heart and think about the future generations the next time you vote."', '"Future,Time,Heart"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"As a small business owner myself, I talk to so many other business owners who delay seasonal hiring by waiting until the last minute to make their temporary hires."', '"Business,Myself,Waiting"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Holiday hiring is only useful if you get the right people, and the consensus among HR professionals is that the most consistent and efficient means of finding good people is to use word of mouth. Namely, this is because focusing on referrals means that only people who are already within your network will apply."', '"Good,Good People,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"On Friday, October 28, 2016, the FBI disclosed that they were reopening Clinton\'s email probe, and the same day, gold hit $1280/oz. Conversely, oil dropped by $1.33 to $45.34 per barrel, while stock prices also took a tumble."', '"Day,Gold,Email"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Historically, there hasn\'t been a significant correlation between gold prices and U.S. elections. Furthermore, history has shown that gold prices tend to fall just before U.S. elections and rise immediately after, and this goes on until the next election."', '"History,Gold,Election"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Investing in gold is one of the wisest decisions that you can make as an investor.', '"Gold,Decisions,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"In most countries, a lopsided election represents a mandate that the winning party could then use to implement their agenda, but the U.S. political system seems to have been made to prevent such an occurrence."', '"Political,Winning,Election"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"While the public school rewards failure by throwing more government money at failing school systems, the voucher system does the opposite."', '"Failure,Money,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Sure, if you\'re a well to do family, you always have the option of sending your children to private schools where teachers spend less time disciplining kids and more time teaching them. However, this option is beyond the reach of most households. And this is what makes school vouchers such a promising solution for lower and middle income families."', '"Family,Time,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Trump is more conservative on individual rights, domestic issues, economic issues and defense. On the other hand, Clinton is quite liberal and wishes to open the borders for more trades and more immigrants."', '"Conservative,Open,More"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Derogatory against women - it seems that Trump is not too keen about having women around him, maybe except for his wife and daughter."', '"Women,Wife,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"No connection to the average voter - Clinton has an air of superiority. Despite her wide smile and pleasant appearance, she is envisioned as someone who is trying to hide something all the time."', '"Smile,Time,Connection"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Trump wants to build a wall at the border of Mexico, while Clinton wants to tear down all walls."', '"Down,Build,Walls"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Social media has changed our lives forever. Some continue to reject social media, refusing to become one of the sheep, but you just can\'t avoid it."', '"Social Media,Media,Sheep"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"A 2014 study commissioned by Facebook and done by Deloitte suggests that Facebook alone contributes almost $150 billion directly to the global economy, and when you add the peripherals, it nears $227 billion."', '"Alone,Done,Global"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'A writers\' ring is where a group of four or five authors agree to promote each other\'s work on their own websites and via their social media outlets such as Facebook and Twitter.', '"Work,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"In 1960, John F. Kennedy rode a superior televised debate performance to victory over Richard Nixon."', '"Victory,Debate,Performance"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"As a real estate investor, you\'re ultimately accountable to you and your checkbook. Of course, you will need to stay on top of your local coding regulations and ordinances. But once you get the hang of it, you really shouldn\'t have any problems with ordinances."', '"Problems,Will,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Getting into the residential investment business entails lots of renovation work.', '"Work,Business,Investment"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Every entrepreneur knows how agonizingly difficult it is to make the decision to give it your all, knowing that failure is inevitable; the successful ones know that the only way to get back up is through learning from that failure."', '"Failure,Learning,Decision"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Blogging can generate a great deal of traffic to your online business.', '"Business,Great,Traffic"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"By having a blog, you can make yourself very accessible to your target audience. You can leave comments open on your blog so you can learn exactly what your audience likes about what you\'re doing with your business and about what they think you should change."', '"Change,Business,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"By taking the time to learn how to blog properly, you\'ll be doing your business an incredible favor, as you will be able to drive a lot of business to your website for your blog."', '"Business,Time,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'It\'s an error in judgment to bounce into starting a small business before you cash in on building a strong foundation.', '"Business,Foundation,Building"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"There is enough of free-of-charge software available on the Net to ease building internet websites and contact pages, as well as implement email marketing campaigns."', '"Internet,Building,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Before you start a business, careful planning is in order to obtain to where you ought to be. The biggest part is to ensure that, once you might have created your own plan, that you simply take motion. Without motion, you are unable to succeed."', '"Business,Start,Planning"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The truth is, there are many types of businesses that require thousands of dollars to be invested during the startup period. However, there are also many different types of business models that you can run from the comfort of your own home without having to reach too deep into your wallet."', '"Truth,Business,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'The best part of owning a blog is the fact that you are in control. You can write about anything you want to write about. You can decide how your blog looks. You can decide who to target. You can decide how to monetize the blog. You have full control!', '"Best,Control,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Many people think that being a graphic designer means going to an expensive art school and buying expensive software that will cost you thousands of dollars. This is so far from the truth. There are hundreds of online education centers that offer top-notch graphic design training.', '"Education,Truth,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Many people decide to jump from niche to niche, as they cannot find success immediately with the niche that they have chosen for their online business."', '"Success,Business,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"When you are starting to run an online business, you need to narrow down a niche market and be able to stick with it until you have a good profit coming in. This can take a while, so you need to have a great deal of patience to make sure that your business is moving in the right direction."', '"Patience,Business,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"It is incredibly important to set goals for your business, as if you have no direction for your business, your online business will be a failure."', '"Business,Failure,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Together, the Jenner sisters have left their mark on the jewelry and fashion accessories industry, first with The Kendall & Kylie Collection at PacSun in 2012, the Metal Haven jewelry collection in 2013, and a line of shoes and handbags for Steve Madden in 2014."', '"Together,Shoes,Jewelry"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Cash flow is a problem for a small and developing company, and the lack of it is the reason why many small businesses fail. Ensure that you have enough money in your bank account to make you able to carry out daily basic needs for your business."', '"Business,Money,Daily"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"It is surprising how little most small business values the customers. A positive feedback from the customer is critical to your business, and what\'s more important is their referral."', '"Positive,Business,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The first aspect of a business that you need to make it work well is money. Once the money aspect is flowing, you can freely work on other aspects."', '"Work,Business,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Can you imagine being Leonardo Da Vinci in the 1400s trying to describe his ideas for machines that would allow humans to fly to the average person of his time? This is hundreds of years before the invention of electricity, the internal combustion engine, and many other things we take for granted today."', '"Time,Today,Fly"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Almost anything worth doing involves some measure of risk - from learning to ride a bike, moving to a new city, and certainly, starting your own business. The point is that no one has ever started a business or created a new product with a guarantee of success."', '"Success,Business,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The economic costs of starting your own business can be significant; in fact, most new startup companies fail because of undercapitalization."', '"Business,New,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"Being an entrepreneur does, of course, give you greater freedom than someone who is tied to a fixed work schedule, but you\'d be mistaken to think that you\'re going to have it easier than your 9-5 counterparts."', '"Work,Freedom,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"I grew and learned, journeyed and understood, that someone who is afraid of failing won\'t get anywhere, and someone who dares to do it runs the risk of failure if they don\'t learn, correct their mistakes, and get back up."', '"Failure,Mistakes,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"The day you decide to pursue your dreams, don\'t forget that this is a game you don\'t enter to compete, but to win. And there will always be someone booing you in the stands, and everything you accomplish could be jeered and hissed at. This is a game between two that you have to win for the people who came to watch you be triumphant."', '"Dreams,Your Dreams,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', 'Anyone who is afraid to lose isn\'t ready to win.', '"Lose,Win,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbc', '"For an entrepreneur with \'improbable\' and \'impossible\' dreams, the alleged stability that comes from getting \'a real job\' is nothing but a sign of slavery."', '"Dreams,Impossible,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', 'I\'ve got nothing to complain about. I have to enjoy and be grateful. Lots of people would like to be in my shoes.', '"Shoes,Grateful,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', 'I think polo players are at their best in their 30s. You\'ve got the talent and the experience. You play with your head - you learn to lose and how to win.', '"Best,Experience,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"We have the best sporting event in the world in polo, and yet it is weak."', '"Best,World,Polo"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"In Argentina, we\'re surrounded by polo ponies. The farm covers roughly 170 hectares, and there are no cattle or sheep, just horses."', '"Sheep,Argentina,Surrounded"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"I\'m usually woken up by the birds and by my schnauzer, Rafa - for me that\'s the best start to the day. I jump out of bed, throw on some clothes, and race to the polo ground."', '"Best,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"We have two trainers at the polo ground and do a mix of aerobics, gymnastics and stretches before we start riding. As polo players, it\'s very important for us to keep in shape. We do a bit of yoga and Pilates sometimes, too."', '"Start,Important,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"Buenos Aires is less than an hour\'s drive from the ranch, and in the evening, we might meet friends for dinner there. I get recognised a bit, but I\'m lucky that polo isn\'t as popular as other sports."', '"Sports,Evening,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"When I was 12 or 13, I realised I was good, but I never knew how far I\'d get."', '"Good,Never,How Far"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"When you get on a good horse, you just know. They are powerful, they stop quickly, they can turn in both directions, and they are fast."', '"Good,Fast,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"Thanks to my father, we were always in good horses."', '"Good,Father,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"I\'ve seen a lot of great players that couldn\'t get to the top because of horses, and I\'ve seen a lot of normal players that got higher and higher because of horses."', '"Great,Normal,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbd', '"If you don\'t have good horses, it\'s very tough to win."', '"Good,Tough,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"The popularity of rugby definitely grew in South Africa over the World Cup, and sport has great power, so hopefully it will make some difference. Even if it\'s just 1%, it\'s a bit of a change."', '"Change,Power,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'If you have heart and you are ready to work hard you will reach your dreams.', '"Dreams,Work,Heart"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"As nines in our system, we need to make sure that we come off the line and that we have numbers correct on both sides."', '"Numbers,Need,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"The massive thing that has changed for me was the game management aspect. I still get it wrong sometimes, we all do, when to attack and when to kick, how to control the game, speeding it up and slowing it down. Whereas I used to just go flat out, as hard as I can, get the ball out and get to the ruck as quick as possible."', '"Me,Game,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'You need to be aware of what you\'re putting on social media and what you\'re talking about.', '"Social Media,Media,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"When we were younger, my brother and I would go out bow hunting. That got me into it. We hunted all kinds of wildlife - things with big horns normally. Deer, kudu, stuff like that."', '"Me,Big,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"I miss hunting and when I go home I always find an opportunity to go for a hunt again, out in the bush veldt."', '"Home,Opportunity,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"A World Cup is always a bit of a watershed for teams, so there will be new faces and players given the chance to perform at a higher level."', '"Chance,World,New"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'You can always improve as a player; there\'s never a time when you can say anything is perfect.', '"Time,Perfect,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'I just always play in a South African speedo when I play for the Springboks.', '"Always,Play,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"Growing up at school I played a lot of fly-half and a lot of scrum-half, I thought I had a good boot but never really used it as much as I do now."', '"Good,School,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"One of my goals is to become the perfect player but you\'ll never reach that goal if your mindset is not right, I think."', '"Goals,Perfect,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"I enjoy putting teams under pressure, forcing turn-overs and just being a pain really!"', '"Pain,Pressure,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"We all say we enjoy playing rugby, but most guys don\'t really show it - and some guys I don\'t think actually enjoy it. So every time I arrive in the morning, I\'ve always got a smile on my face. Once I lose that enjoyment, I will stop playing."', '"Smile,Time,Morning"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"I\'m pretty excited when I get a good kick up in the air and our wings start chasing, because I know it\'s a 50-50. When you kick well and compete well, the odds fall on our side."', '"Good,Wings,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'You can have size but to be physical is a different story.', '"Story,Size,Physical"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'I play to inspire people and give confidence to young kids who might shy away because of their size.', '"Confidence,People,Shy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'A charity approached me to help raise awareness for testicular cancer and there are now some great photos of famous South Africans in their pants helping to spread the word.', '"Great,Famous,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'When I joined Sale I thought that if I did well there I would have a chance of making the World Cup squad. What I did not expect was how quickly I got back into the frame.', '"Chance,World,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"It\'s good if people see me as a running nine but I wanted to be viewed as an all-round scrum-half, who can do anything at any time."', '"Time,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"The South Africa public are very passionate and they just care a lot for their team. So if something goes wrong, because they are so emotionally invested in it, they feel as though we are letting them down."', '"Care,Feel,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"I\'ve always had lots of energy; it\'s just been about channelling it in the right way. I know I can be annoying, but that\'s just my way and hopefully more people than not like my personality."', '"Personality,Energy,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'It is not just willy-nilly running around. I need to fill certain spaces and make sure we are covered on both sides of the ruck and the numbers are right.', '"Numbers,Right,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"A multi-racial team with a black captain means a lot to the country. There will always be negative political parties in South Africa, but hopefully it\'s something to take forwards."', '"Black,Political,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', 'You need to adapt your game for what the team needs.', '"Game,Your,Adapt"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcbf', '"At Sale we\'re an up and coming club, wanting to draw bigger crowds. You can\'t just run everything, though, you need a balance."', '"Balance,Everything,Coming"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I am a bad boy. I don\'t come across clearly to a lot of people, so I am bad for them."', '"Bad Boy,I Am,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I love the forest. It is the place where you hear yourself better.', '"Love,Yourself,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"For me, \'Diamond Necklace\' is a commercial attempt, as it has songs and glamour."', '"Me,Glamour,Necklace"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I enjoyed working on \'Maheshinte Prathikaram.\'', '"Enjoyed,Working"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"When I listen to a basic thought, I try to visualise the cinema in it. Sometimes it is dark, sometimes boyish, sometimes amateurish. It is a trial and error method. But the bottom line is that I want to entertain the audience."', '"Cinema,Sometimes,Dark"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"It\'s the failure of my debut film which made me an actor, which made me want to succeed in the industry. But that doesn\'t mean I regret whatever choices I\'ve made over the years. No, not even \'Kaiyethum Doorathu!\'"', '"Failure,Regret,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"The less people know about you, the more you understand how beautiful life is. It\'s good when you exist only on screen. I don\'t want them to take me home. I love to have my privacy."', '"Life,Love,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I am not affected or carried away by success or failure.', '"Success,Failure,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"You can probably ask any actor: every time you start a new film, it\'s literally like your first movie. Everyone, regardless of the filmmaker being a debutant or a veteran, takes their time to settle down when you begin the shoot together. It\'s like all of us have moved into a new house, and we are setting up the place."', '"Time,Together,New"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I want to entertain viewers as much as possible.', '"Possible,Want,Entertain"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I am an actor, and I would like to reinvent myself through every character that I portray."', '"Myself,Character,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I have never been 100% confident that I am right about anything.', '"I Am,Never,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"My thought process is in Malayalam. So, every time I have to work outside Malayalam, the process is a little stressful. I have to translate my Malayalam thoughts into English and back to Tamil."', '"Work,Time,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"The closest encounter I had with films in my childhood was sitting on the lap of my father at a shooting set, and he would say \'rain,\' and it started raining, and then he would say \'song,\' and people started dancing. I thought I was sitting on God\'s lap."', '"God,Rain,Childhood"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I wasn\'t really sure about the kind of films I wanted to be a part of. That\'s when I saw \'Aaranya Kaandam.\' I was stunned; it was such a stylish film.', '"Stylish,Film,About"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I feel that entertainment happens when fact and fiction is balanced.', '"Feel,Entertainment,Happens"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I thoroughly enjoyed shooting for \'Velaikkaran,\' and I made a great friend in Sivakarthikeyan during the process. Also, it was wonderful working with director Mohan Raja. I have not seen a director who takes so much effort to get things the best way possible."', '"Best,Great,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Roles don\'t fascinate me. It is the narrative, the screenplay that is fascinating."', '"Me,Narrative,Fascinating"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"All I believe in is, you need to be yourself."', '"Be Yourself,Believe,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"When you are talking about human emotions, stardom doesn\'t matter."', '"Emotions,Matter,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Whenever I have really enjoyed being part of a film, it has worked well for me."', '"Me,Well,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I think everything is temporary.', '"Everything,Temporary,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I would like to do movies of all genres.', '"Movies,Like,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I would like to look funny on screen, doing comedy."', '"Funny,Look,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"When I choose the scripts, all I look forward to is an impressive narration."', '"Look,Choose,Forward"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"The five directors in \'5 Sundarikal\' experimented, and it was a very personal exercise. Amal, Anwar, Aashiq, and Sameer have done things that they have never done before. Debutant Shyju has also made a beautiful film."', '"Beautiful,Exercise,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"When I began acting, my biggest fear was whether the audience will appreciate the kind of films I do."', '"Fear,Will,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I want my films to make money first. Awards and all can come later.', '"Money,First,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I don\'t expect to win awards while working in films.', '"Win,Awards,Expect"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I will continue to do films that excite me.', '"Me,Will,Continue"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"In Malayalam, I can improvise, and acting is easy because I think in Malayalam, but for \'Velaikkaran,\' I had to prepare for a role, which is a first for me."', '"Me,Acting,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I listened to the script of \'Carbon\' at the end of 2014. I liked it the moment I heard it. I wanted to do it.', '"Moment,End,Carbon"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'Most of the films that I do help me learn something.', '"Me,Help,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I try to choose characters that don\'t remind the audience of my previous roles. I make a conscious effort for that.', '"Effort,Choose,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"If I had my way, I want to do 15 films in a year, but I have realised I cannot physically do that."', '"Way,Year,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'All I want to do is to make movies that are appealing to people.', '"Movies,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I know it\'s a big gamble, but I want to do good films."', '"Good,Know,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"My father hasn\'t backed me in any way, and I don\'t think anybody has backed me."', '"Me,Father,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'Working with Thiagarajan Kumararaja in \'Super Deluxe\' was absolutely mind-blowing.', '"Super,Absolutely,Working"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I often see only my mistakes. I always feel I could have done better. Every artist goes through it.', '"Better,Feel,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I like movies made by Spike Lee - doing those films out of the U.S., that is really daring."', '"Movies,Doing,Daring"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I never wanted to be an actor but ended up being one.', '"Never,Up,Actor"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I have been fortunate to collaborate with people who have been open to discussion. If I tell them something, they have always explained to me why they want it the other way."', '"Me,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Mohan Raja is an interesting filmmaker. He is constantly, if I may use the word, contradicting himself. He explains a scene, and then he will try to break that and rebuild it. That, to me, is filmmaking. Every scene is constructed after a lot of discussions."', '"Me,Filmmaking,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Every character, when it comes to a cinematic representation, gets complicated and layered. You are given a lot of dimensions than a single dimension to an individual. That\'s the main difference between seeing something out of the window and seeing something on screen."', '"Character,Window,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"If I do a film, I go to the place where it is based on, interact with people, and then, I believe, you pick up things without you even noticing."', '"Believe,People,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'It is easier to produce a film on your own than convincing another person to come on board.', '"Person,Own,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"There are two kinds of films: the ones that are devoid of logic but can still hijack the audience, and those that can win them over with logic. Both kinds can succeed, and I like to work in both."', '"Work,Win,Logic"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I\'ve done only things I\'ve liked, and I\'m happy that others have liked them, too. I hope it keeps going that way. But l would never want to do films which please just one set of audience; they should connect with everyone."', '"Hope,Way,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Offscreen, I\'m a private person. I\'m shy and don\'t know how to face the public."', '"Face,Shy,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I\'m not a person who goes out of my way to change my look. I like my characters to look as natural as possible.', '"Change,Look,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'It feels good to hear good things about yourself.', '"Good,Yourself,Good Things"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I\'ve always wanted to do a role based on a real-life person.', '"Person,Always,Role"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I think it would be a dream for any actor to play someone like Changampuzha.', '"Someone,Dream,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I am a person who doesn\'t like responsibility of any kind. But I do enjoy what I do.', '"Responsibility,I Am,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I\'m an actor who evolves once the shoot starts.', '"Shoot,Actor,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I do only what I like. If we do something we don\'t like, we will become someone else."', '"Will,Someone,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I don\'t know how to be professional. But I always enjoy what I do.', '"Know,Always,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I will happily sit at home and take care of the house.', '"Home,Care,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I trust my directors to see me through, for I don\'t consider myself as a natural actor - or a good one at that."', '"Trust,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I believe that anyone with a bit of guidance can act.', '"Believe,Guidance,I Believe That"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"The only thing my famous last name got me was a foothold in the industry. That was the easy part. The biggest problem is survival. As Fazil\'s son, I am expected to know everything - acting, dancing, horse riding... I am not trained in all these, and I don\'t think I ever will be."', '"Famous,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I have grown up seeing success and failure.', '"Success,Failure,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'Failure affects me hard.', '"Failure,Me,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"People expect star kids to be perfect - horse-riding, fighting."', '"Fighting,Perfect,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I want the audience to watch my films, and that is what I value more than any awards."', '"Value,More,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'It doesn\'t matter to me how I look on screen. What matters to me is how I connect with the audience.', '"Look,Me,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'Failure is part and parcel of the process of experimenting with roles and films.', '"Failure,Process,Parcel"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"My films may not have a great opening, but I am not bothered about it. Whatever the numbers be, I want those viewers who come for my films to be excited about watching the movie."', '"Great,I Am,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"Mistakes happen, and then you try to overcome those. I like that process."', '"Process,Mistakes,Overcome"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I give my best to each role that I do.', '"Best,Role,Each"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'People often ask whether marriage has changed me. I didn\'t marry because I had to change.', '"Change,Marriage,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I have always maintained that the audience should take a call on this. Its up to them to decide whether they want to see a pirated version or not. They should understand the effort and amount of hard work that go into a film.', '"Work,Hard Work,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"I want my films to do the talking. I feel if people have to understand me better, I should do more good films. I just want them to know me through my films."', '"Good,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'Let me make something clear: I can\'t do anything in particular to make others laugh. I do what is necessary for a character. The body language of the character may make others laugh.', '"Character,Me,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"When I am with my friends, I am comfortable."', '"I Am,Comfortable,Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'I like to laugh and to make people laugh.', '"People,Laugh,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"The characters I portray are an extension of what I\'ve seen, heard, or read, and so what you see in my films are how I understand life."', '"Life,See,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', 'What I look for in a project is whether the storyline excites me.', '"Look,Me,Project"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"As an actor, you create a character from your understanding of what you have heard and your observations. Eventually, every film is an extension of the images that I have seen or what I have heard or read somewhere."', '"Character,Understanding,Create"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc0', '"People know me through my characters. I don\'t think they have any idea about the individual that I am. They know I am a director\'s son, and I am married to an actress."', '"Me,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc2', 'The inventory goes down the elevator every night.', '"Night,Down,Elevator"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc2', 'Advertising is what you do when you can\'t go see somebody. That\'s all it is.', '"See,Advertising,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc2', '"There is no such thing as a Mass Mind. The Mass Audience is made up of individuals, and good advertising is written always from one person to another. When it is aimed at millions it rarely moves anyone."', '"Good,Mind,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', 'I always get the \'goth girl\' thing because I wear black. But I don\'t worship death.', '"Death,Black,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', 'I got beat up up in Texas because my bootlaces were the wrong color.', '"Beat,Wrong,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', '"I want love, because love is the best feeling in the whole world."', '"Love,Best,Love Is"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', 'My family is basically Gypsies - for real.', '"Family,Real,Basically"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', '"People don\'t talk to me the way they would other people. They kind of look at me, but they never come over. It makes me feel like there\'s something wrong with me."', '"Look,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', 'I do think I tend to have a darker nature than most.', '"Nature,Think,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc3', '"I\'m beginning to get pigeonholed as the girl who plays the crazies and weirdoes - and that\'s not the entirety of who I am. Hopefully, the whole point of being in this profession is that you change into anyone you want to be."', '"Change,I Am,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc5', 'Time is a dressmaker specializing in alterations.', 'Time', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc5', '"Character builds slowly, but it can be torn down within incredible swiftness."', '"Character,Down,Incredible"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc5', '"You cannot contribute anything to the ideal condition of mind and heart known as Brotherhood, however much you preach, posture, or agree, unless you live it."', '"Heart,Mind,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc5', 'Sometimes there is a greater lack of communication in facile talking than in silence.', '"Communication,Silence,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc5', 'One of the dreariest spots on life\'s road is the point of conviction that nothing will ever again happen to you.', '"Life,Road,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"Faith is not a sense, nor sight, nor reason, but taking God at His work."', '"Work,Faith,God"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"When I first met Big, we were both at a \'Bad Boy\' family photo shoot. I was kind of familiar with the name Biggie Smalls, but I really wasn\'t that much into hip-hop at the time, so I really didn\'t know that was him. He said he didn\'t even know I was an artist on \'Bad Boy.\'"', '"Family,Time,Bad Boy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"Big will always be a part of my life. But I\'m still on this Earth, so I have to live my life for now and the future."', '"Life,Future,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"Certainly it is a blessing to have three beautiful kids who are all healthy. God put them here for me to nurture and bring them up and try to keep as close to right as I can. So it\'s a blessing. It\'s a big responsibility, but at the same time it\'s an honor."', '"God,Time,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', 'I don\'t have time to sit up and write songs all day. Maybe one day when my kids get older.', '"Time,Day,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"I\'m really an inner spirit that only makes itself known through the music. A lot of people think I\'m an introvert, or quiet and moody. I\'ve even heard some people say that there\'s a certain mystery or darkness about me. I\'m not that way. I\'m just really into what I do."', '"Music,Me,Darkness"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"My childhood was limited to mostly gospel music. We didn\'t have, like, a lot of records in our house, you know. It was like my grandparents who raised me. They were pretty old-fashioned in their religious ways, so it was like church, church, church, school, school, school."', '"Music,Childhood,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"I\'ve certainly had to go through trying to change the fact that I was always identified as the widow of Notorious B.I.G. You know, I\'m never going to be able to get away from having been married to him, but that\'s not what identifies me. You know, my life isn\'t just about that."', '"Life,Change,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"People used to say my son looked like a Mexican Biggie. And when he was first born, memories of Biggie... you know, we didn\'t always have the greatest days. For at least half the length of our marriage we were separated, so everyday was definitely not a good day."', '"Good,Marriage,Memories"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"I guess you kind of got to realize that once you in a marriage, whatever it is, you gotta deal with it. Not necessarily that you got to accept it, but you have to deal with it and try your best to make it work for you, for the both of you."', '"Work,Best,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', '"I can mourn internally, just be quiet about it. I have my moments but I\'m not a real, expressive person, especially when it comes to like sadness."', '"Real,Person,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc6', 'My business issues are just that - business - and I deal with them like they are business.', '"Business,Deal,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"I love playing moms. It\'s a lot easier than being a mom, I hear."', '"Love,Mom,Hear"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', 'I haven\'t actually spoken to my parents since the hurricane.', '"Parents,Hurricane,Since"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"One thing I think kids need to do is more chores, and take care of their own rooms. Responsibilities are really important to start them with. If they have animals, they have to feed them and care for them. That\'s the only way I think I could do it."', '"Care,Way,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"I have a friend that has five kids and she went through a trial separation with her husband, and she didn\'t have time to be upset. Every now and then, she\'d call me on the cell phone and just cry."', '"Time,Me,Cry"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"My theory is, if you can do comedy and you can be in a scene with someone like Brad Garrett and hold your own, you\'ve really got a future in this business."', '"Future,Business,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', 'I think comedy is one of the hardest things to do.', '"Comedy,Hardest,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"It takes a lot of energy to work, in general, especially if you\'re the lead in something."', '"Work,Energy,Lead"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', 'Usually when you\'re working is when people want you to work. They don\'t want you as much when you\'re not working. That\'s the frustrating nature of our business.', '"Nature,Work,Business"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', '"When I was in school, I was very involved with a lot of things. I was very very active. I couldn\'t say that I wasn\'t popular. I was a cheerleader when I was in junior high. I didn\'t make it in high school so I started a dance line."', '"Dance,School,Active"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc7', 'My mother keeps me abreast of all the hometown things.', '"Me,Hometown,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'The foundation of family - that\'s where it all begins for me.', '"Family,Me,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"It\'s okay to take time for yourself. We give so much of ourselves to others and we need to be fueled both physically and mentally. If we are in balance, it helps us in all our interactions."', '"Time,Yourself,Balance"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'There are things I\'ve done in the past I\'m not proud of - and I could talk about them if I wanted to - but I don\'t reveal my secrets... I prefer certain things to remain personal; there have to be boundaries. And I don\'t think you need a scandal to have an interesting story.', '"Past,Secrets,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I think beauty comes from within. If you\'re happy and look at life in the best way you can, even when there are problems, it can make you beautiful on the outside."', '"Life,Beauty,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"When I wake up in a bad mood, I try not to stay in one. Learn to make the best of what you have."', '"Best,Mood,Bad Mood"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I\'m such a happy, easygoing person."', '"Person,Happy,Easygoing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I\'m a very independent woman.', '"Woman,Independent Woman,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Everybody wants you to do good things, but in a small town you pretty much graduate and get married. Mostly you marry, have children and go to their football games."', '"Good,Graduation,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"We\'re raising our girls to understand the real meaning of Christmas, and to know that it\'s most important to have Christmas in your heart. We go to our local mall and donate toys, and we say prayers for all the people in the world who might not be as lucky as we are."', '"Christmas,Heart,World"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'Nashville is one of the greatest places for the best songwriters in the world. It\'s been fantastic to live there and to raise our family there. It\'s a great town.', '"Best,Family,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I don\'t want to sound like a Hallmark card, but to be able to wake up each day with food and shelter, that alone is good. Forget aging and the fact that my butt is becoming a little more familiar with my knees than my tailbone. If you are six feet above ground it\'s a good day. So, give me more!"', '"Alone,Good,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I think I\'m a lot like other moms out there who feel like if we don\'t have the pecan pie we have every year, then it just won\'t be Christmas."', '"Christmas,Feel,Year"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I know one of the reasons God gave me kids was to test my patience.', '"Patience,God,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I don\'t let things go unless I\'m ready for them to go.', '"Go,Ready,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"A little bit of stage fright, then I\'m ready."', '"Stage,Ready,Stage Fright"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'It\'s not complicated to embrace life. You just have to make the choice.', '"Life,Choice,Complicated"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Shania Twain brought a whole other fan base to country music with her sound, the way the videos were produced."', '"Music,Way,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Country music fans are extremely supportive. Once they\'re with you, they\'re with you for life."', '"Life,Music,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Reba is very, very close to everyone around her. She\'s a classy lady."', '"Classy,Lady,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I don\'t know why \'happy\' can\'t be a story.', '"Know,Happy,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Marriage isn\'t something you agree to do one day, and if things don\'t go right, then it\'s over."', '"Marriage,Day,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I think what makes our marriage work amid all the glare is that my husband is my best friend. He inspires everything in my life and enables me to do the best that I can. I want to hang out with him more than anyone.', '"Life,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I have had wrinkles on my forehead and my smile line since I was a kid. I see them in my own kids. I know what they\'re going to look like. So it\'s kind of like that\'s my personality. I feel the older you get, too, the more confident you become just in your own skin."', '"Smile,Personality,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I\'ve always defended Shania. She not only opened doors; she knocked several down.', '"Doors,Always,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'Nashville was totally different than I ever dreamed. I had only seen the music business on television and been to a couple of concerts. I had no clue.', '"Business,Music,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"Children are easily influenced, and I always want to do things I can be proud to show my kids someday."', '"Children,Proud,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'My goal as an artist is to always be true to who I am and give my fans music they will enjoy for a lifetime.', '"Music,I Am,True"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'Country music is the people\'s music. It just speaks about real life and about truth and it tells things how they really are.', '"Life,Truth,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"When you\'re a mom and you have three children, nothing bothers you. Trust me. Who cares what people say? I\'ve got other things to deal with."', '"Trust,Mom,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I didn\'t realize that everyone was so attracted to my hair. I thought, well what about my music?"', '"Music,Hair,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I wasn\'t a great background singer.', '"Great,Singer,Background"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"The song This Kiss was definitely my breakthrough song. After that, Breathe was my breakthrough album."', '"Song,Kiss,Breakthrough"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I\'m a home girl. I like to stay home.', '"Home,Girl,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I\'m very competitive but in a very nice way.', '"Way,Nice,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I\'m still proud of what I\'ve done, even if it hasn\'t been the biggest song on the radio or hasn\'t gone to number one."', '"Song,Done,Proud"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'A man who is right by your side through everything makes you happy. But he can leave your side to make dinner once in a while!', '"Man,Dinner,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I constantly work at maintaining balance. For me, my family comes first. If my family is taken care of, then everything else usually falls into place."', '"Work,Family,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I try to find a reason to laugh each day. Somehow, if you can incorporate laughter into your day, every day, it really helps. It\'s the little things in life that make me happy."', '"Life,Laughter,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"When you\'re a mom to three children, nothing bothers you. Trust me. Who cares what people say? I\'ve got other things to deal with."', '"Trust,Mom,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"There was a period of time when I first moved to Nashville, like the first couple of years, that I was just simply lost. I didn\'t know who I was; I didn\'t know really what I was doing here. I was meant to be a singer, but I just felt lost. That\'s when I went on the search for my birth family."', '"Family,Time,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I can\'t even say what my greatest fear is because I, I can\'t even imagine. Being without my family... I can\'t even say it because it makes me cry."', '"Family,Fear,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I think society, in general, is hard on women, period."', '"Women,Society,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'The hardest thing for me is planning ahead. My mom was brilliant at it.', '"Mom,Me,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I grew up asking for everything under the sun for Christmas, but I knew I wasn\'t going to get it all."', '"Christmas,Sun,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I have a wonderful family: My parents are churchgoing, salt-of-the-earth Southern people. They gave me a lot of love and are so unaffected by fame."', '"Love,Family,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I\'m able to shift gears from mom to performer to mom pretty quickly.', '"Mom,Gears,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"To be honest, I didn\'t really understand how involved putting a fragrance together could be - or would be. Once I made the choice to actually do it, I just went for it. I just dove in and have really learned a lot about putting a scent together. It\'s kind of exciting."', '"Together,Fragrance,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'My family and my friends are most important to me. These people are my foundation.', '"Family,Me,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"This may sound funny, but I feel my most beautiful when I\'m clean, fresh out of the bath. I don\'t have to be dressed up. I could be in comfy clothes at home hanging out with my family."', '"Funny,Family,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I drink a lot of water and I never leave the house without putting on moisturizer and lip gloss.', '"Water,Never,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"The only album that I listen to upon recording a new one is my \'Cry\' album, because sonically, I think it\'s my best album to date. But other than that, I\'ve never listened to my records, ever."', '"Best,New,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I love \'Somebody to Love\' by Queen and of course \'Bohemian Rhapsody\' is one of my favorites, just because it makes everyone in the room go crazy. Everyone tries to sing along with it, and half the room gets it right and the other half gets it wrong."', '"Love,Queen,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I have this strength that comes from knowledge.', '"Strength,Knowledge"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', '"I was adopted into this incredible home, a loving, positive environment, yet I had this yearning, this kind of darkness that was also inside me."', '"Positive,Home,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc8', 'I have worries and fears just like everybody else. But I have every reason to wake up each morning and be very happy.', '"Morning,Wake Up,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc9', '"I adore burgers. I know they are bad for me, and only technically a sandwich, but a well made burger, juicy and hot off the grill, is wonderful!"', '"Me,Hot,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc9', '"Humans are insane. We kill our own people, starve our own people, sell them, work them to death, beat them, don\'t give them affordable/free/good healthcare, and let them live in misery, while a few of us have - we have all we want. We are evil."', '"Work,Death,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc9', '"There are lots of antagonists in the \'Jane Yellowrock\' series, but one stands out as uber-evil to me, and that is Lucas DeAllyon."', '"Me,Out,Lots"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcc9', '"Shelter dogs are the most loving, wonderful, sweet pets in the world. They understand being rescued, loved, and protected. The hubs and I have 2 rescued 11-yr-old Pomeranians, who adore us."', '"Sweet,World,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I know I always had a lot of energy growing up and I had to put it somewhere. Theater allowed me to really feel things, to laugh, to cry, to explode outward. I could do anything and it was totally accepted and appreciated. If I hadn\'t gone into the theater, I probably would have been a psychotic killer."', '"Me,Energy,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', 'I certainly went to New York because I was searching. Most people who go to New York are searching.', '"New,People,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"Usually I like playing other people. I like finding myself through other characters. But when you do cabaret, you are yourself. I think it\'s the most fun, and I tell you, if somebody had told me that, I would have done it fifteen years earlier than I did."', '"Myself,Me,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I\'ve got all these great broads in me, all these character women. I was playing a torn-down stripper at twenty-five on Broadway, and now I fit the shoes."', '"Women,Great,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I\'m from the South, so I tend to tell stories. That\'s how we express ourselves."', '"Tell,How,Express"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', 'My happiest times in the theater are when I do ensemble pieces. I really got into theater because of that closeness.', '"Because,Happiest,Pieces"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I don\'t like to read reviews. Even the good ones you start to analyze: \'Oh, did I do that? I have to make sure I do that again.\'"', '"Good,Start,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I\'ll tell you something: my dad was a nuclear engineer and he was really bright, and I\'ve always said that because of negotiating at such a young age with my dad, it was really such a gift because I could then negotiate with very difficult personalities - and not end up being the scapegoat. I learned to really pick and choose my battles."', '"Age,Dad,Gift"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"Sometimes directors may not give you words, you know? They may not talk at all! You\'ve just got to use your radar to figure out how you can get to the center and not lose yourself, but still be directed at the same time."', '"Time,Lose,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"Half of me is this wacked-out comedienne who will do anything for a buck and a laugh. Well, at least for a laugh. But the other half is a lot darker, sadder and more pensive. It\'s the dark side that feeds the outrageousness and allows it to surface. I think that\'s true for anyone with comic flair."', '"Me,True,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"Being funny is a symptom of what\'s underneath. You\'re pumping out all that energy because something else is going on inside you, some opposing force, something uncomfortable."', '"Funny,Energy,Uncomfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"All I can say is that I\'ve always felt like a very old soul. When I was 3, I felt 60."', '"Soul,Always,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I\'m a character actress. I\'m the girl next door, the aunt, the quirky cousin. You have to innately know who you are and be happy with that."', '"Character,Door,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', 'I just love kids. I always have.', '"Love,Always,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I have a very \'theatre\' face. I have what they call a wide mask. I probably would have been a big film star in the \'20s with the silent films where they used a lot of key lighting, and make-up carved out your face."', '"Face,Mask,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcca', '"I never like to be the same, whether it be comedy or drama, funny or serious."', '"Funny,Drama,Serious"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I just feel like I\'m the luckiest person in the world being able to do what I love and be able to do it all day every day if I like, you know, I mean it\'s great, I love it."', '"Love,Great,World"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I don\'t think you can create art out of anger; it has to come out of some form of understanding. You have to feel good about who you are and that you could do something to change things.', '"Change,Good,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I had something I was trying to say and sometimes the message is an easy transmission and sometimes it\'s a difficult one but I love the power of saying it so I\'m gonna do it whether it\'s hard or easy.', '"Love,Power,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"There were a lot of stop signs in my life... People telling you what to do, when to do it, and so on."', '"Life,My Life,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I have always wanted to tell my story - or, more to the point, my side of the story."', '"Always,Story,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"The reason why I began making quilts is because I wrote my autobiography in 1980 and couldn\'t get it published because I wanted to tell my story, and my story didn\'t appear to be appropriate for African-American women."', '"Women,Why,Story"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Children are so talented. Little children, until about the age of 10 or 11, are just little artists. They need to be given the time and the space and the materials to do their work. That\'s all they need."', '"Work,Space,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Paintings, people really don\'t understand... They don\'t really get paintings. Quilts they do understand because everybody has a quilt in their house."', '"People,Understand,House"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"What has not changed is people are still doing whatever they think they can get away with. I think there\'s still a lot of advancement for people, generally speaking, to learn to let other people live in the world with freedom."', '"Freedom,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I think all children love art, but not all get the opportunity to do it."', '"Love,Art,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I was functioning in a time when people were struggling, and they knew they had to struggle, and I was a part of that struggle. It wasn\'t just women."', '"Women,Time,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Art is a form of experience of the person, the place, the history of the people, and as black people, we are different. We hail from Africa to America, so the culture is mixed, from the African to the American. We can\'t drop that. It\'s reflected in the music, the dance, the poetry, and the art."', '"History,Experience,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I had this idea that I wanted to do this mixture of visions of African American women and visions of African American men. And call it \'The Men\' and call it \'The Women\' and show different faces of these two people.', '"Women,Men,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Because the mask is your face, the face is a mask, so I\'m thinking of the face as a mask because of the way I see faces is coming from an African vision of the mask which is the thing that we carry around with us, it is our presentation, it\'s our front, it\'s our face."', '"Vision,Thinking,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I guess I had fun doing it but it has hard memories for me.', '"Memories,Me,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I think that has been a benefit to me because I think most people understand quilts and not a lot of people understand paintings. But yet they\'re looking at one.', '"Me,Looking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I\'m not so presumptuous to feel that they\'re gonna get it right away, get exactly what I have in mind. I hope that they\'ll enjoy looking at it at any rate, whatever it is. And that\'s why I started writing stories on my work."', '"Work,Hope,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"I can recall that nobody ever went out the door that wasn\'t dressed nicely, even though it was the Depression. I particularly remember on Sunday, the day we all went to church, if you didn\'t have it together, you kind of stayed in the house."', '"Together,Day,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"There were people who would complain about their jobs, and my mother would walk away from that job. I liked that a lot about her. She was a very, very creative woman, and eventually, she stopped working outside the house, and she just had her own customers whom she made clothes for."', '"Walk,Woman,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'Black women have never embraced feminism. They didn\'t embrace it in the \'50s and \'60s; they\'re not embracing it now. That\'s not new. I think it\'s a tendency among women in general not to be supportive of each other.', '"Women,Black,New"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Different people were complaining, and I remember saying, \'Why don\'t we just demonstrate?\' The Whitney was the first."', '"Remember,People,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Every time people struggle, they survive, they do better, and then they forget, and they end up back where they started from."', '"Time,Struggle,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'It is so sad that it takes so long for people to understand what needs to happen in order to be free.', '"Sad,Long,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', '"Here I come with these images of black and white people, and a lot of people got angry at me."', '"Black And White,Black,Angry"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccb', 'I think I had struck on a combination of imagery and politics that worked.', '"Politics,Think,Combination"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Hours after I gave birth to my first child, my husband cradled all five pounds of our boy and said, gently, \'Hi, Sweetpea.\' Not \'Buddy\' or \'Little Man.\' Sweetpea. The word filled me with unanticipated comfort."', '"Man,Me,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Did you know you\'re supposed to soap and scrub for as long as it takes to sing \'Happy Birthday\' twice?', '"Birthday,Long,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Mother\'s Day is a bittersweet day for many of us. We all have mothers, but some of us have lost them."', '"Day,Lost,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Manspread, mansplaining, manterrupting - all of it, whether conscious or not, diminishes women\'s voices, minds, and bodies."', '"Women,Minds,Whether"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Women are blessed with lots and lots of extra ways to win or lose validation. If you\'re a woman, you\'ll be judged on your beauty and your wit and how often you smile. You\'ll be judged on how much hair you have in some places and not in others."', '"Smile,Beauty,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"The custom of clasping hands is thought to date back thousands of years, as proof of not holding any weapons."', '"Hands,Back,Proof"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I entered my egg-freezing adventure from a feeling of lack - a lack of fertility, of the right partner, of biological time. But this perceived lack actually produced abundance - of options, time, peace of mind, and microscopic chances of a child."', '"Time,Peace,Peace Of Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Shaking hands is a pretty good way to get yourself sick, not necessarily with Ebola, but with a million other germs that can cause colds and flu."', '"Good,Yourself,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'My first husband and I never came close to having kids.', '"Never,Husband,First"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I know how much sleep I need, how much time on the elliptical I need, and how much chocolate that buys me."', '"Time,Me,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'The option to freeze one\'s eggs is just about the most empowering choice a single woman who knows she wants to be a mother can make.', '"Woman,Choice,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"No longer is a geek identifiable by a pale complexion, black-rimmed glasses, a bowling shirt that says \'Nerd World Order.\' No, geeks are everywhere. And they\'re cool!"', '"Cool,World,Shirt"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"The desperate hunger our president has for approbation has led him to such lengths as claiming that God stopped the rain during his Inauguration. In fact, Mother Nature made sure it rained on Trump\'s hair the minute he started his speech."', '"Nature,God,Rain"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'My husband is a graduate of two Ivy League universities - with a degree in Classics! - and he sounds like a David Mamet character when I hear him on a business call.', '"Business,Character,Degree"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I once accidentally \'replied all\' and sent an email complaining about my then-boyfriend to a bunch of strangers. It was meant for my friend who was a bride, but I ended up addressing her entire wedding party. Her marriage lasted; my relationship didn\'t."', '"Relationship,Marriage,Wedding"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Are we a people who put politics over integrity? Or are we a country of voters and leaders, men and women, husbands and wives, fathers and mothers, colleagues, humans who care about treating each other with basic dignity?"', '"Politics,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"If you\'re ever bcc\'d, do not go near \'reply all.\' \'Bcc\' is \'blind carbon copy.\' It means you\'re a fly on the wall, dude! If you hit reply all, it\'s beyond bad etiquette to out the person who gave you the superpower of invisibility. It\'s like screaming, \'I\'m a spy!\'"', '"Fly,Bad,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Contrary to the negative stereotype that folks who swear have poor vocabularies, a fluency in taboo language correlates with overall verbal fluency. The more words you know, the more you know... and the more colorfully you can express yourself, with nuance, metaphor, and emotion."', '"Yourself,Negative,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"We all think Al Gore invented email so we could save time and save paper, to save trees. And that includes phone trees."', '"Time,Phone,Email"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'It was my husband who had to open all the baby shower gifts which were haunting me in their candy-colored gift wrap - thank you notes demanding to be written.', '"Me,Gift,Shower"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Twerking takes its place in a long line of dance moves deemed immoral, even apocalyptic. The waltz was called sinful because it demanded dangerously close contact between dance partners. In 1914, the tango earned a papal denunciation for being \'damaging to the soul.\'"', '"Soul,Long,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Harassment doesn\'t just happen to \'social observers\' and \'comedians\' - women who express themselves publicly are reliably verbally attacked online and in person, not for their substance but for their form."', '"Women,Person,Harassment"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I\'m squandering invaluable gray matter by censoring myself.', '"Myself,Matter,Gray"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"By the time I got to college in the \'90s, virtually every young woman I knew was on the pill. It was like a rite of passage, along with Doc Martens and Take Back the Night rallies."', '"Time,Night,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I spent my late twenties and all of my thirties figuring out what I was supposed to be doing and where my home was.', '"Home,Late,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m a snowflake. And so are you. Your children are snowflakes. And so are mine. And those who protest the loudest about not being snowflakes? I can see your six-fold ice crystals from here! Because every person, empirically, is unique."', '"Children,Unique,See"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Divorce court seemed to inspire in my girlfriends 1940s-era fashion fantasies, not only for me, but for themselves."', '"Me,Fashion,Inspire"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"If you grasp the bathroom door handle to exit without using a paper towel, you\'re right back where you started, with who-knows-whose germs on your hands."', '"Door,Hands,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'ve always wanted, notionally, to be a mother. And I was certain I would be, because everyone I know, gay or straight, married or single, rich or not so much, who truly wants to have a child figures out a way, some way, to have one - whether through adoption, fostering, surrogacy, fertility, accident, or persistence."', '"Persistence,Gay,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Wildfires can leave the land with burn scars that last for years.', '"Scars,Burn,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I don\'t mean to brag, but my water filter curates tap water, offering moi the finest combination of H, 2, and O available."', '"Water,Filter,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I remember my mom sitting at our kitchen table, paying bills with a small smile. She\'d sigh and say, \'I\'m so blessed to be able to pay these.\' She knew it was about what you have."', '"Smile,Mom,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Here\'s a simple guideline: if five names or fewer are cc\'d, just go nuts and hit \'reply all.\' But if more than five folks appear in the cc line, pause. Give it a thought. Some people are promiscuous and cc dozens of people who don\'t need to know each other\'s business."', '"Business,Simple,Pause"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I am an approval junkie.', '"I Am,Approval,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Nothing ages you more immediately than being called \'Mrs.\'', '"Nothing,More,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Just as kids need to learn to respect their elders, we are a society that increasingly respects our youth."', '"Respect,Society,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"When I was a kid, we called every teacher, every parent - anyone over the age of 20, it seemed - \'Mr. or Mrs. so-and-so.\'"', '"Age,Teacher,Parent"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'ve spent my life being responsible, building a career, and waiting to find the right partner with whom to start a family."', '"Life,Family,Waiting"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I think there\'s something very disingenuous about literally all people who say that they don\'t care about anyone\'s approval.', '"Care,People,dont Care"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Any responsible essayist or memoir writer who\'s writing about herself is not just saying, \'Here\'s what happened,\' and opening up her diary. There needs to be consideration of other people\'s feelings."', '"Diary,Feelings,People"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I\'ll never get complacent. I am my own toughest critic.', '"I Am,Never,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"There\'s a bit of a reluctance on my part to promote myself as any kind of hero because the things I\'ve had to overcome in my life are not the deepest, darkest things."', '"Life,Myself,Hero"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Power is not nearly enough for Trump. Power he already possessed, starting with the money his father gave him, which grew into the money he never paid in taxes because he is \'smart.\' No: Power and ambition pale in comparison to Trumpbeth\'s rapacious grab for applause."', '"Money,Power,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'A leader who cobbles together his self-esteem by attempting to silence or libel his critics and by amplifying his echo chamber is a dangerous one indeed.', '"Together,Silence,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Approval ratings matter for politicians, largely for good reason. A leader with plummeting approval ratings ought to take note of the needs and hopes of his people."', '"Good,People,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m writing a book, and there\'s not even space for a desk in our home. So I spent my hard-earned book money and rented the small apartment downstairs from us."', '"Space,Money,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"\'Man cave\' seems retrograde, but \'she shed\' seems progressive. Or maybe it\'s just a place for me to eat embarrassing amounts of chocolate in private."', '"Man,Me,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Women all over this great land are creating spaces just for themselves, most often out of sheds in their backyards. They\'re fantasy cottages, bespoke bungalows, \'mama maisons,\' if you will, for mothers and wives who need a sanctuary - a haven where they can do anything, or nothing."', '"Women,Great,Mama"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"As a mother, I don\'t want any girl twerking near my kid at a bat mitzvah."', '"Mother,Bat,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:36:00', '2023-05-29 11:36:00'),
	('388974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"In case you don\'t watch much TV or spend time with anyone under 40, \'Really?\' is pop culture\'s pithiest way to deliver a withering put-down."', '"Time,Culture,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m not actually perishing, but I do feel like I die a little every time someone uses \'literally\' to mean \'really.\'"', '"Time,Die,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Adverbs, we know, are meant to modify a verb, an adjective, or another adverb. They help us understand things more clearly, more vividly, more... morely."', '"Help,Know,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Scientists have discovered that, as we age, our brains act like computers with fuller and fuller hard drives. So when we\'re trying to recall a fact or a word or a name, it takes us longer, because - to put it scientifically - our brains hold a lot of \'stuff.\'"', '"Age,Computers,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m no scientist, but I\'ll dare extrapolate and say that it\'s pretty obvious that the more you struggle to recall something, the smarter you are!"', '"Struggle,Dare,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"John Travolta is getting old, despite what his hair is trying to tell us."', '"Hair,Trying,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'This is America; our icons are complicated.', '"America,Complicated,Icons"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Wanting to be loved and appreciated connects us all.', '"Loved,Us,Appreciated"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I tell my kids all the time that I\'m so lucky they chose me to be their mom.', '"Time,Mom,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"If you don\'t know what mansplaining is, or manterrupting or manspread, then you\'re probably a guy."', '"Know,Guy,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Social media provides a constant platform on which to feature what we deem beautiful, meaningful, and worthy."', '"Beautiful,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I think the curation consternation is this: Just because you like something or list something, are you really curating?"', '"Just Because,Because,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'One man\'s content is another woman\'s crap. And the crappy content - let\'s call it crontent - will never go away.', '"Man,Woman,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"The fact that oversharing exists at all as a noteworthy notion is a relief, because I\'m afraid that our younger generations could grow up having no idea what it even means to overshare."', '"Grow,Afraid,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'It\'s beyond TMI - oversharing is not just too much information; it\'s incessant sharing of non-information - breaking news about your gluten-free diet complete with duck face selfies.', '"Diet,Face,Duck"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Not that I\'m any good at it, but the beauty of meditation is that it liberates us from our own thoughts."', '"Beauty,Good,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"To my knowledge, there are, pretty much, two ways to be interesting: One is to actually do interesting things, achieve the remarkable. The other way to be interesting is to be interested, curious about the world and about other people - not relentlessly revelatory about yourself."', '"Knowledge,World,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Despite amazing advances in fertility to help older women get pregnant, the complications, increased chances of autism, and chromosomal abnormalities are significant considerations."', '"Women,Amazing,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Mothers of all ages delight in their children, but I don\'t know that, if I were younger, I would feel as acutely, profoundly, preciously grateful for every smile, squeal, and - yes - diaper blowout."', '"Smile,Grateful,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"If I could have had my baby sooner, I would have, simply to spend more years with him."', '"More,Baby,Simply"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m an old mom of a young baby, and every moment matters."', '"Mom,Moment,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Snowflakery is simply being human, which makes it a pretty flakey insult."', '"Being Human,Insult,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'It\'s fitting that an insult largely aimed at youth has made children of those who use it. \'Snowflake\' reminds us how much we need climate change... in politics.', '"Change,Politics,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I\'m not proud that, in my time, I\'ve tried to harness the power of prayer to fit into a pair of jeans."', '"Time,Power,Prayer"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Having grown up Catholic, my prayers were scripted - memorized and deployed in church and before bed. As a young adult, I veered off script and talked to God more plainly. And by \'talked to,\' I mean that I basically asked for things to turn out the way I wanted them to."', '"God,Way,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('388999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"They say there are no atheists in foxholes, and in the foxhole of my divorce, I found solace in walking to St. Patrick\'s Cathedral and lighting candles."', '"Walking,They Say,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'I asked God for a healthy baby. An answer arrived in my daughter.', '"God,Daughter,Answer"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Famous people I\'ve interviewed - powerful people, brilliant people, people whom you look at and think, \'Seriously, do you not have pores?\' - have turned to me after interviews and asked, \'Was I okay? I hope I was okay.\'"', '"Hope,Famous,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Approval makes the world go round, even if many of us want to transcend our hunger for it."', '"World,Go,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'For weeks I ran through a mental inventory of my closet. Did I want to wear something new - to christen it and forever make it The Divorce Dress?', '"Dress,New,Forever"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Whenever I told women - friends or acquaintances - that I had to go to divorce court, they\'d invariably, without skipping a beat, ask, \'What are you going to wear?\' It was like instant female solidarity: of course it mattered what I was going to wear."', '"Women,Solidarity,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"On a meaningful day, everything you wear can have meaning. It becomes what I wore That Day, whether that day is a beginning or an end."', '"Day,Beginning,End"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Am I an elitist because I like wine?', '"Wine,Because,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I have no problem being full-term pregnant and do not understand women who say, \'I can\'t wait to get this baby out of me!\'"', '"Women,Me,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Whether you plan to labor with an epidural or the Pitocin Fairy pins you down or you end up having an emergency C-section, there are still choices you can make throughout your entire birth experience that allow you to feel some control over what is probably the most dramatic day of your life."', '"Life,Experience,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Getting a pedicure seems to be a standard pre-birth ritual, presumably because it is relaxing and makes you feel pretty even though your little piggies are going to be covered in those awesome no-skid hospital socks which I kept on for three days."', '"Hospital,Feel,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Well-done eyelash extensions make you look beautiful and doe-eyed without a lick of makeup.', '"Beautiful,Look,Makeup"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"If you want to become a mother, you can. I promise. It may not happen the way you think, but it\'s possible. It just takes a combination of a little planning and a lot of living your life."', '"Life,Way,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Most of my best friends had children in their early 40s.', '"Best,Children,Early"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Donald Trump, who surely has lots of high-stakes issues on which to focus, is consumed with the appearance of women."', '"Women,Focus,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Making fun of people\'s looks is something that children do - mean children - and, in fact, linguists have determined that Trump actually speaks like a 3rd grader."', '"Fun,Children,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'It\'s one thing to decry and defy political correctness in the name of efficiently achieving clarity or revealing an honest truth. But it\'s quite another thing entirely to support name-calling and nastiness.', '"Truth,Political,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'People who champion Trump say they don\'t want politics-as-usual. But \'politic\' is also an adjective. It means \'tactful and diplomatic.\' It\'s necessary for an elected official to be politic.', '"Champion,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"The t-shirts that declare \'Girls Rule the World\' offer an empirical falsehood, but at least the aspiration is there."', '"World,Offer,Aspiration"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Boys have always known they could do anything; all they had to do was look around at their presidents, religious leaders, professional athletes, at the statues that stand erect in big cities and small. Girls have always known they were allowed to feel anything - except anger."', '"Anger,Look,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'The boy taught from infancy to be tough is emotionally doomed.', '"Tough,Boy,Taught"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', 'Sometimes art helps illuminate science.', '"Science,Art,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I don\'t think, in my entire 18 years as a student, I ever used an exclamation point in an academic paper."', '"Paper,Point,Student"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"I admit I feel funny when I use the word \'whom\' as I\'m talking to my diapered children, but I persist."', '"Funny,Children,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccc', '"Real love is more than a one-time, seemingly iron-clad pledge that we will never be apart. If you\'re over 20, you\'ve probably figured out that meaningful love isn\'t constricting; it doesn\'t chain you to one place or to each other."', '"Love,Love Is,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccd', '"\'The Replacements\' is where I met Jon Favreau, and we just clicked like, you know, like kids at a camp."', '"Know,Like,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccd', 'One of my favorite guys when I was young... I\'ve always loved Bill Cosby. I\'ve always wanted to direct him in something.', '"Young,Always,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fccd', '"\'The Replacements\' is where I met Jon Favreau, and we just clicked like, you know, like kids at a camp. And he wrote my next movie, which was \'Made.\'"', '"Know,Next,He"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"I was a dancer for about 14 years. I was a martial artist for the same amount of time. I quit that when I realized I should probably not get my nose broken anymore. I love trying new stuff. Now I\'m loving archery, and I surf. I just like to explore new things, I guess. I\'m a big kid!"', '"Love,Time,New"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"I was born in East Germany, before the wall came down. We sort of escaped, I guess. I grew up all over the place. Germany, London, back and forth between Minnesota and Germany. I was sort of an army brat, but not in the army."', '"Back,Place,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"My mom was a huge fan of \'Dirty Dancing.\' I couldn\'t quite get a break, and she was like, \'Patrick Swayze was a dancer!\' And Fred Astaire. I started dancing, and it led me to acting. It helps with fighting or whatever choreography in general."', '"Mom,Me,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"Every show finds its groove, I would say. The first season is the season to figure out the dynamics, the workflow."', '"First,Groove,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"I think Hollywood wants to be safe. The things you do first become your calling card, and I think people just sort of go, \'Well, we know he can do that.\' They kind of put you in that hole."', '"People,Safe,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd0', '"To be honest with you, I\'ve been dying to do a nice indie feature - just something about a regular guy with a big quirk or a big emotional problem. Just something that\'s a straightforward, classic indie film. It sounds weird, but it\'s been easier for me to get cast in big tentpole films than the indie community. I\'d love to do that."', '"Love,Community,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I consider myself a woman. I happen to fall into the transgender category, but I rather describe myself as a woman first."', '"Myself,Woman,Transgender"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I looked up the Queen of Swords and I read the meaning. It was a tarot card. The description of the tarot card sounded to me like the description of a certain type of woman: She\'s strong, she\'s proud, she\'s intelligent and all these different things. I was like, that\'s how I want to be."', '"Me,Queen,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"You\'re brought up not to hit girls, that it\'s the worst sin, and that\'s what I do. But you know, gender is the last thing I think about when I\'m fighting. It\'s the one situation where I don\'t think of gender at all."', '"Fighting,Situation,Gender"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"For the rest of my life, my testosterone levels will remain underneath women who were born with female anatomy. There\'s no advantage I could ever get by not taking estrogen. Which I\'m not doing, I\'m just saying that\'s a fact, so people should realize that. Which, I don\'t think most people understand."', '"Life,Women,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'The danger is you never know if people are actually saying what they mean. I\'ve learned you never know how someone will react.', '"People,Will,React"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Some people believe I have an automatic advantage over other female MMA fighters, so they think \'well she has to be stronger, because she used to be a male,\' but if they look into the science of it and what the hormones do to the body, to the male body once taken over a period of time... it dissipates."', '"Science,Time,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'Winning a pro tournament is another step toward getting fights against higher-ranked opponents.', '"Step,Winning,Tournament"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Do you ever wonder what the Amazons would have looked like in real life? I think in MMA, like, you see it - that warrior spirit. You see that determination. You see that heart. You see that bravery."', '"Life,Heart,Determination"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Matt Mitrione went well beyond disagreeing with the medical experts who say I should be able to compete as a woman, and personally attacked me as a fighter, as a woman, and as a human being."', '"Medical,Me,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"These past six years, people have seen me as a woman, not a transsexual. People in the gym, people I train with, it\'s been great, it\'s been awesome. I\'m just a woman to them. I don\'t want that to go away. It\'s unfortunate that it has to."', '"Great,Me,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"The testosterone levels of a normal male can be anywhere from 300-1,000 nanograms. For the average female, it\'s 10-70. Mine is around 7."', '"Mine,Normal,Average"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'For years I\'ve known at some point it\'s very likely the shoe would drop. Maybe someone would guess that I\'m trans. Maybe they would know me from my life before I transitioned.', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"If no one knew that I was trans - let\'s say that I made it very, very far. Let\'s say I went to the UFC and became a UFC champion, even, won the belt title, took it home and no one ever knew - that would be great for me."', '"Home,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I\'m a legitimate fighter who trained for years for this and I\'m good, but suddenly, just because I\'m a transgender woman, I fall into the category of \'freak show.\'"', '"Good,Woman,Fighter"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I was built to be a fighter, to be a warrior just like Ronda Rousey was built to be a warrior and Bruce Jenner is getting back to being the hardcore person, the warrior that he is."', '"Fighter,Back,Warrior"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Media is set up to give information to the people - at least that\'s what it says. But we all know in the U.S. that media is a capitalistic system, people are getting paid to write things, they have bosses and editors, and they have bosses, and they put pressure on people to write intriguing stories that catch the eye."', '"Information,Media,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I want the public to know how it feels, the fear of being scrutinized, of being outed. The fear of what happens when you come out and the media puts you under a microscope. It\'s crippling. You get lost."', '"Fear,Lost,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I\'m very good at submissions from the ground. I have good takedowns and good striking, so I\'m pretty well-rounded."', '"Good,Ground,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I was looking for a way to lose a little weight and discovered MMA and its disciplines, and I fell in love with it."', '"Love,Lose,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'Getting choked out feels a lot better than getting knocked out.', '"Better,Out,Than"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'But I got into MMA for the sport. I love fighting.', '"Love,Fighting,MMA"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Around 19, I got a girl pregnant. I really didn\'t want to get married, but I was raised with the belief to marry that person and take care of our child."', '"Care,Person,Take Care"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"My role models are every single woman that steps inside of the cage - inside of an octagon, inside a ring, or on a mat - and proves to themselves and to others that they can do what they need to do. Those are my heroes. Those are my sheroes. Those are the people that I look up to."', '"Look,Woman,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Where I came from, it was more shocking to be an atheist than to be transgender."', '"Transgender,Atheist,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'Transgender women especially feel like we have to fit the binary system to a T in order to not be recognized as trans.', '"Women,Feel,Binary"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'It took me about a year to understand and to feel the support from the transgender community.', '"Community,Me,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I expected that someone was going to out me; you just can\'t go through life with a microscope on your career without someone delving into your past a little bit.', '"Life,Me,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"If the UFC would listen to reason on transgendered athletes, it could help change the sport for the better."', '"Change,Better,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"It\'s hard because the phrase \'woman trapped in a man\'s body\' is thrown around a lot, but that\'s like shorthand. It\'s deeper than that. There\'s so much more to it."', '"Man,Woman,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I think when kids are younger, they don\'t have these preconceived notions of what a transsexual person is."', '"Person,Think,Younger"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"MMA is the most dangerous sport there is for a transgender, with all the body contact, I know that."', '"Body,Transgender,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I\'m female. I\'m human. Sometimes I dominate and sometimes I\'m dominated.', '"Sometimes,Human,Dominate"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Right after I got out of the military, I realized that I wasn\'t surrounded by men all of the time. I started behaving - and outwardly - how I truly felt inside. And I decided that it would be a good idea if I transitioned."', '"Time,Good,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I break people\'s faces. I break their arms. I break their legs. That\'s a part of the sport. That\'s my job. That\'s the job of the opponent who\'s trying to do the same thing to me.', '"Me,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I was brought up with the idea that God is watching at all times.', '"God,Watching,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I felt like I was going to hell just for putting on women\'s clothes.', '"Women,Hell,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'The first time I got called \'Miss\' that felt amazing.', '"Time,Amazing,First Time"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I miss being able to throw down with other elite-level women, to be considered among the best."', '"Best,Women,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I remembered watching the first UFC. You couldn\'t get it on TV. They were doing it bare knuckles. No gloves. I wanted to do that.', '"Watching,Doing,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"Playing devil\'s advocate with myself is very, very hard. It\'s a 24-hour thing. Because I know there\'s a possibility that people are going to come after me, they\'re not going to understand me, so I have to be ready."', '"Myself,Devil,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I don\'t believe that a transgender fighter should have to disclose her personal medical history to other female fighters before they fight.', '"History,Medical,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I did wrestling in high school; that helped, as far as technique goes."', '"School,Far,High School"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'The techniques that you learn as a male fighter are the same techniques you learn as a female fighter.', '"Fighter,Same,Learn"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I remember when I first came out, it was like half and half, half the female fighters were like, \'I understand why she did it, and I\'ll fight her,\' and half said I shouldn\'t be in the cage and said horrible, horrific transphobic comments about me."', '"Fight,Me,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I see similarities between Jackie Robinson and myself.', '"Myself,See,I See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I like playing video games in my spare time.', '"Time,Video Games,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I\'m the first transsexual fighter in MMA. Like, ever. It\'s always going to be part of the narrative, but I\'ll deal with it. I\'ll try my best to use it to my advantage."', '"Best,Fighter,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I\'d rather be known for my talent, for what I can do in the cage. I\'m sure that will come."', '"Talent,Will,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"If I don\'t take estrogen hormone replacement therapy, I can get osteoporosis."', '"I Can,Get,Therapy"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I do not have a competitive advantage when fighting another woman.', '"Fighting,Woman,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I wanted my private life to be private. I just wanted to be a fighter.', '"Life,Private Life,Fighter"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I would say to those kids that were like me not to give up.', '"Me,Up,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I train almost every day. It\'s like work.', '"Work,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', 'I want to compete against some of the best female fighters in MMA. That\'s my goal.', '"Best,Want,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd1', '"I was pretty sure, going along the timeline, I was going to have to embrace being a role model for transsexuals in mixed martial arts, and I\'m willing to embrace it - of course."', '"Role Model,Embrace,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I can dance, a little bit."', '"Dance,I Can,Little Bit"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Every time I play darts I try to keep my poker face on and stay focused until that last dart has gone in.', '"Time,Face,Stay Focused"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I don\'t look like the stereotypical darts player, do I?"', '"Look,Like,Darts"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"When you play with the men, you know they don\'t give up."', '"Men,Know,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"The sky is the limit now, us women are showing that we can beat men and hopefully it will open more doors."', '"Women,Men,Sky"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"As long as you put the effort in with your practice, the muscles in your arm stay relaxed and mental preparation is all it takes."', '"Effort,Long,Preparation"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"To any young women out there who might be thinking about taking up darts, I would just say, \'Go for it.\'"', '"Women,Thinking,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Spider and heights are much easier than beating a man at the Ally Pally, any day of the week!"', '"Man,Day,Spider"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'My son is always up early.', '"Son,Always,Early"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'m not going to dwell on what someone has said if it doesn\'t affect my life. I think that attitude helps to strengthen my character.', '"Attitude,Life,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Trolls online are constantly giving you sexist comments.', '"Comments,Online,Giving"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I\'m just me, a normal person."', '"Me,Person,Normal"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I feel really proud of myself for helping to put the ladies\' game out there.', '"Myself,Game,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I never get really nervous.', '"Never,Nervous,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"If I\'m in a pressurised situation, I\'ve learned to breathe, chill myself out and be calm."', '"Myself,Chill,Calm"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I definitely think I can use the crowd to my advantage.', '"I Can,Use,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'There\'s more women who can play like me if not better and we just need more recognition really.', '"Women,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Us women can beat these men, we just need more opportunities to prove ourselves."', '"Women,Men,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Who\'s to say I can\'t beat anyone?', '"Beat,Say,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I\'ve made history, I\'ve just beaten one man, who\'s to say I can\'t beat more?"', '"History,Man,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Being included in just the U.S. Darts Masters was amazing enough but to now be able to go worldwide is something I could only dream of.', '"Amazing,Enough,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'m so proud to help put women\'s darts on the map.', '"Women,Help,Proud"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'The sport has come on - we do not just play in pubs any more and there are massive international competitions.', '"More,Play,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"In the sport itself it\'s fine, but online I have had constant sexist comments saying women are not as good as men."', '"Women,Good,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I practise about three to four hours a day and I will play one night a week, or at the weekend in a competition."', '"Night,Competition,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I feel I can concentrate a bit more on playing darts now people are just seeing an equal playing field.', '"Feel,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I know I\'ve probably got a massive target on my back now, because everyone wants to be better, to beat me."', '"Me,Better,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I started playing when I was about 16, and I got picked for the England youth team when I was 17 because I was doing quite well. It\'s all spiralled from there."', '"Youth,Doing,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"When I was 15, I used to go with my sister to her youth games because she was really good."', '"Good,Youth,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'It sounds really bad but I never actually wanted to play.', '"Bad,Never,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'m just a normal person.', '"Person,Normal,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Every little bit of hate just gees me on to do better and prove them all wrong.', '"Hate,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"It made me a stronger person, and more determined. I don\'t know if I\'d still be as strong if I didn\'t have all that hate. I needed hate to make me more determined."', '"Hate,Me,Stronger"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'The men I\'ve played are all respectful and gentlemen towards me. I\'ve never really had a problem. In the past a lot of people would go: \'We\'re playing a woman.\' But now they\'re thinking: \'We\'re playing a good player.\'', '"Good,Men,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Against the men I have a point to prove. So I have more determination whereas, when I\'m playing the women, we know each other\'s games so well. I need that extra boost just to prove to the men we can compete against them."', '"Women,Men,Determination"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I have helped darts in general.', '"Darts,General,Helped"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Especially with the ladies\' game, I have proved we can compete with all these men."', '"Men,Game,Compete"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"We just do not get the recognition or the opportunity to play against these men, so obviously you don\'t see it that often."', '"Men,Opportunity,See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I don\'t see myself at a physical disadvantage.', '"Myself,See,Disadvantage"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'The women\'s game has come on leaps and bounds.', '"Women,Game,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I got a lot of criticism online and a lot of harsh comments.', '"Criticism,Comments,Online"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I have learned from experience with the BDO and the ladies tournament.', '"Experience,I Have Learned,Tournament"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I focus on each leg and not what the score is.', '"Focus,Score,Leg"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Nando\'s is my pre-match meal. I have the butterfly chicken, mash and coleslaw."', '"Butterfly,Chicken,Meal"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I haven\'t taken into account how much I drink. I do drink a lot when I am on stage anyway. You will see me come back and have sips of water. I haven\'t taken into account how much.', '"Water,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I\'ve beaten two of the best players in the world, and if that doesn\'t say that women can\'t play darts I don\'t know what can."', '"Best,Women,World"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'If I saw negative comments I tried to look past them.', '"Look,Past,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Ally Pally has been amazing for me.', '"Amazing,Me,Ally"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"About six months after I had my little boy in April 2014, I ended up getting a kidney disease."', '"Boy,Disease,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I started taking medication to weaken my immune system because that is what was attacking my kidneys. The problem was when I went on different medication, I suffered side effects. And the side effects caused \'moon face,\' where my face swelled up. It was a reaction."', '"Moon,Face,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"When I play on stage, I have to drink a glass of water."', '"Water,Glass,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'m constantly drinking a lot of water to flush my kidneys out. That helps my body.', '"Water,Body,Drinking"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"My son is going to grow up looking at the newspaper cuttings and thinking, \'Wow, my mum did this.\'"', '"Thinking,Grow,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I don\'t even know what a feminist is.', '"Know,Even,Feminist"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I am a normal person from Milton Keynes.', '"I Am,Person,Normal"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"If I can be a role model and leader, I am happy to do that."', '"I Am Happy,I Am,Role Model"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I try to help people as much as I can.', '"People,Help,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I hope I\'ve done women\'s darts proud, put women\'s darts on the map and given it the recognition that it deserves."', '"Hope,Women,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"There are women who can play at my standard, if not better, and they can beat men, too, so it would be nice to see them do it as well."', '"Women,Men,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I had a lot of negative comments, but it made me stronger and made me want to do more in my game. It made me more determined if anything."', '"Me,Game,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'ve got good family support.', '"Family,Good,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I think I\'m a person who just makes things better.', '"Better,Person,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I think I\'m an enjoyable person to be around.', '"Person,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I haven\'t set myself any goals or targets because I am taking each day as it comes. But who is to say that I can\'t be a world champion, or do anything that I put my mind to?"', '"Myself,World,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I know how to zone myself in and just play the game.', '"Myself,Game,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'ve always had darts around me growing up because my family has always played it.', '"Family,Me,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'When I started playing darts and watching more darts on TV I would say someone like Trina Gulliver definitely inspired me to carry on and keep playing.', '"Me,Watching,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Us women, we can play darts."', '"Women,Us,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"When I went to Q school, I was walking into a tournament where 500 other players all wanted the same thing as me."', '"Me,Walking,School"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Whatever happens in women\'s darts in the future I will be able to think I helped to achieve it.', '"Future,Women,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"When women play men, it brings out our better game."', '"Women,Men,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"I could be two sets, two legs down but I wouldn\'t think that. I take each leg as it comes."', '"Legs,Down,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'Can I eat bugs? Yes no problem.', '"No Problem,Eat,Problem"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I don\'t take any notice of negative stuff said on social media. If anything it spurs me on more.', '"Me,Social Media,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"You always get the odd comment, along the lines of the women are not as good as the men, and I get called a lesbian."', '"Women,Good,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'No man wants to lose to a woman.', '"Man,Lose,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I don\'t have time to sit at home and not do anything. I used to just sit there and just watch TV and eat crisps. Now I don\'t have five minutes to do that.', '"Time,Home,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"Once I get up on stage, I will have to forget who I am playing and focus on the game itself."', '"Focus,Game,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', '"It\'s nice if I am called a role model, because I never thought that I would be a role model for anyone else."', '"I Am,Role Model,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I\'m quite proud that I\'ve inspired so many people.', '"People,Proud,Quite"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'If people want to put the pressure on me that fine but I don\'t put pressure on myself - that is where pressure comes from.', '"Myself,Me,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'The more the women beat the men hopefully that will bring up more opportunities for us and then the possibilities are endless as to what can happen.', '"Women,Men,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd2', 'I don\'t look at it as a man\'s sport because the women play as well. It\'s an open sport.', '"Women,Man,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I\'m intrigued by the dark. Out of darkness comes creation.', '"Darkness,Dark,Creation"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'Disneyland is supposed to be the happiest place on Earth and I have to say when I\'m riding around in that crazy Space Mountain ride I\'m happy.', '"Space,Ride,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'Triple tonguing? It was sort of invented. It wasn\'t in the script. It was something that I came up with.', '"Something,Up,Triple"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I started as a model in Holland and Chanel took me to New York when I was 19, after which I decided to stay."', '"Me,New,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'My French is still good. That\'s a beautiful language and I\'m happy to speak it.', '"Good,Beautiful,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'Netflix is something I watch.', '"Netflix,Something,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I think there\'s a big misconception out there about actors and the choices they have.', '"Choices,Big,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I am attracted to the dark side of life!', '"Life,I Am,Dark"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'We\'ve always been ready for female superheroes. Because women want to be them and men want to do them.', '"Women,Men,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"Just because you\'re of the same sex, what difference does it make? Get married to whomever you want."', '"Sex,Just Because,Difference"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I always feel like I want to do my career my own way. I never follow anybody\'s path, what they\'ve done."', '"Path,Way,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I want to work with great directors. I want to work on good material with good actors. I\'ve probably done 20 movies at this point and a lot of independents. It\'s been an incredible ride and I love it and I\'m just going to keep going and doing what I\'m doing.', '"Love,Work,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"It\'s never been important to be a huge star or to have some breakout role. If you\'re the lead, you get a lot more screen time and you get a lot more chances to develop that character more thoroughly than you would if you do it in a little supporting part."', '"Time,Character,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'Robert De Niro... It seemed like a pretty cool thing to do to put his name on my resume next.', '"Cool,Name,Resume"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I try not to have high expectations of people because it just sets you up for disappointment, but it\'s great to work with actors who are that talented and accomplished."', '"Work,Great,Disappointment"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I love scary movies. The Shining and Don\'t Look Now are two of the best.', '"Love,Best,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"Everybody gets typecast in movies, but you have to make wise choices. I\'d say around 90 percent of movie casting is about the way you look, so you have to fight that. If producers had their way, I\'d only be in action films, but I\'m interested in a more varied career than that."', '"Movies,Wise,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I like to go from mainstream movies to more artsy films. I don\'t sign on for the money. Maybe I should, but I don\'t. There\'s always a good reason for doing something."', '"Money,Good,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"The only way to do is just to go for it, otherwise it ends up looking phoney."', '"Looking,Way,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I don\'t know how to cook and there\'s so much work involved you have to buy the groceries and prepare them. I like it when people cook for me, or I\'ll just order some take-out."', '"Work,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I have a friend in New York who\'s a stylist and I went over to her place because she\'s got a lot of clothes. I basically ended up wearing most of it. So it\'s all stuff that I brought over.', '"New,Place,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I love the first two X-Men movies because I thought that Bryan Singer did such a great job. He elevated that whole genre. He\'s a very talented director.', '"Love,Great,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I know Dark Phoenix is a huge part of the X-Men saga, so I\'m assuming they\'re at least going to want to touch on it, but I don\'t know and I don\'t know whether I would want to be involved. That depends on many different things."', '"Dark,Know,Touch"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I live in New York. I don\'t really particularly want to move to LA.', '"New,Live,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I\'m trying to fight typecasting as hard as I can, while I have time."', '"Time,Fight,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"Once you achieve a certain level of success or fame, it becomes really difficult to go against type."', '"Success,Difficult,Fame"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"If you do well as an actor, a good director will pick up on it, and keep it in the film."', '"Good,Will,Good Director"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I don\'t watch TV.', '"Watch,TV"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"There\'s certain things I try to avoid, as an actress, just to keep my world from being as narrow as it could be."', '"World,Avoid,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'The Dutch are a very practical people.', '"People,Practical,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I personally like to do independent films.', '"Independent,Like,Personally"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I like the work that I get to do.', '"Work,Like,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I\'m 5\' 11 as I proudly say - just so I don\'t have to say six feet.', '"Feet,Say,Six"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"As a European I had fit in almost seamlessly in New York for the last 25 years, but in Oklahoma I stood out like a sore thumb."', '"New,Last,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I love stories about two people who are doing illegal things, who we really enjoy watching despite the fact that we know they are doomed in some way."', '"Love,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"During my first visit, I was really struck by how deeply religious many Oklahomans are. It is a very conservative state and as somebody who grew up in a very liberal country, it was jarring to me at first."', '"Me,Country,Conservative"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"Film has played such a big part in my life, in my impressions of the United States."', '"Life,My Life,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'When someone holds a knife to your throat it\'s easy to be scared. It\'s not hard to imagine what it would be like.', '"Easy,Someone,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I always feel like I want to do my career my own way.', '"Way,Feel,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I never follow anybody\'s path, what they\'ve done."', '"Path,Done,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"The great thing I think when you do independents is that people are really there for the same reason. They\'re not there because they got a lot of money and they want to just go home and get it over with. They\'re there because they believe in the script or the director or the cast or whatever it is, and they want to make it work."', '"Work,Money,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I\'ve lived in New York for a really long time.', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"In studio films, everything has to be boxed in, everybody needs to know beforehand - this is comedy, this is sci-fi, this is drama - and what\'s the point of independent film if you don\'t get to experiment?"', '"Drama,Comedy,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I keep pushing buttons and trying to grow as a person and as a filmmaker.', '"Grow,Person,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I look a certain way. I have a very specific kind of look.', '"Look,Way,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"You don\'t ever know with films. You just hope for the best, but sometimes it\'s a bit of a crapshoot."', '"Best,Hope,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', '"I think every movie is its own little world, and a director certainly sets the tone."', '"World,Own,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd3', 'I enrolled in an acting workshop and my first acting role was on the TV soap opera \'Melrose Place.\'', '"Acting,Place,Workshop"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', 'I am a very frank person and that\'s how I hope to remain. What you see is what you get.', '"Hope,I Am,See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', '"I carry an umbrella when I am outdoors and always wear sunscreen, even when I am sitting in front of a computer screen! I never touch coffee or other caffeinated drinks."', '"I Am,Coffee,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', '"I have nothing to explain. As for being misunderstood, I have grown accustomed to that."', '"Nothing,Misunderstood,Explain"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', 'Awards are not the only markers of success; I don\'t judge myself just based on them. I believe that each cinema-goer has his own mental trophies.', '"Success,Myself,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', 'I always carry lip balm and lipstick. Lipstick is a very important beauty product because I find that lips are the most beautiful feature of anyone\'s face.', '"Beauty,Most Beautiful,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', '"Also, I use facial masks diligently. I use at least two a day - one for moisturizing and one for whitening. I think I go through at least 600 sheets of facial masks every year."', '"Day,Go,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd4', 'I fell in love with dressing myself up.', '"Love,Myself,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd5', 'Progress in civilization has been accompanied by progress in cookery.', '"Progress,Civilization,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd5', '"I certainly feel that the time is not far distant when a knowledge of the principles of diet will be an essential part of one\'s education. Then mankind will eat to live, be able to do better mental and physical work and disease will be less frequent."', '"Education,Work,Knowledge"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"Remember if people talk behind your back, it only means you\'re two steps ahead!"', '"Remember,People,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"Being an only child and losing both my parents at an early age, I have found that the friends I have made over the years are the people who help me get through life, good times and bad."', '"Life,Good,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"Yes, I suffer terribly from depression. I have to work at being happy, it\'s not my natural instinct. My natural instinct is, if something wonderful happens, to throw water in my own face."', '"Work,Water,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"In order to be Miss Anybody you had to have excellent grades, and I had terrible grades because of my dyslexia."', '"Grades,Order,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"I think that people that are not sensitive, who seem to bang through life, do survive, but I don\'t think they get the really soaring feelings that people who are more artistically bent can get."', '"Life,Feelings,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', '"Strangely enough, the first character in Fried Green Tomatoes was the cafe, and the town. I think a place can be as much a character in a novel as the people."', '"Green,Character,Cafe"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd6', 'I have a lot of friends that are ex-Miss Alabamas and ex-Miss Georgias.', '"Friends,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', 'A woman has to be twice as good as a man to go half as far.', '"Good,Man,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', 'It takes a clever man to turn cynic and a wise man to be clever enough not to.', '"Wise,Man,Wise Man"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', 'Some people think they are worth a lot of money just because they have it.', '"Money,People,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', 'Any writer worth the name is always getting into one thing or getting out of another thing.', '"Name,Always,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', 'Sex is a discovery.', '"Sex,Discovery"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', '"I\'m not happy when I\'m writing, but I\'m more unhappy when I\'m not."', '"Unhappy,Happy,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd7', '"Few enjoy noisy overcrowded functions. But they are a gesture of goodwill on the part of host or hostess, and also on the part of guests who submit to them."', '"Enjoy,Guests,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'Nobody\'s free until everybody\'s free.', '"Free,Nobody,Everybody"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'I am sick and tired of being sick and tired.', '"Tired,I Am,Sick"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"If I fall, I\'ll fall five feet four inches forward in the fight for freedom. I\'m not backing off."', '"Freedom,Fight,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'I feel sorry for anybody that could let hate wrap them up. Ain\'t no such thing as I can hate anybody and hope to see God\'s face.', '"God,Hope,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'There is one thing you have got to learn about our movement. Three people are better than no people.', '"Better,People,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'People have got to get together and work together. I\'m tired of the kind of oppression that white people have inflicted on us and are still trying to inflict.', '"Work,Together,Tired"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"I\'d been in jail, and I\'d been beat. I had been to a voter registration workshop, you know, to - they were just training and teaching us how to register, to pass the literacy test."', '"Training,Know,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"With the people, for the people, by the people. I crack up when I hear it; I say, with the handful, for the handful, by the handful, cause that\'s what really happens."', '"People,Happens,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"Is this America, the land of the free and the home of the brave, where we have to sleep with our telephones off the hooks because our lives be threatened daily, because we want to live as decent human beings in America?"', '"Home,Daily,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'Every red stripe in that flag represents the black man\'s blood that has been shed.', '"Black,Man,Red"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"White Americans today don\'t know what in the world to do because when they put us behind them, that\'s where they made their mistake... they put us behind them, and we watched every move they made."', '"Today,World,Mistake"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"On the 10th of September 1962, sixteen bullets was fired into the home of Mr. and Mrs. Robert Tucker for me."', '"Home,Me,Fired"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"We hadn\'t heard anything about registering to vote because when you see this flat land in here, when the people would get out of the fields, if they had a radio, they\'d be too tired to play it. So we didn\'t know what was going on in the rest of the state, even, much less in other places."', '"Tired,Rest,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'What I really feel is necessary is that the black people in this country wil have to upset this apple cart. We can no longer ignore the fact that America is not the... land of the free and the home of the brave.', '"Home,Black,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"They - you know, when we walked in - when I walked in with the two white men that had carried me down - and they cursed me all the way down. They would ask me questions, and when I would try to answer, they would tell me to hush."', '"Men,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'I\'m showing the people that a Negro can run for office.', '"People,Office,Run"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'That\'s why I want to change Mississippi. You don\'t run away from problems - you just face them.', '"Change,Face,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'I know lots of people in Mississippi who have lost their jobs trying to register to vote.', '"Lost,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"I was forced away from the plantation because I wouldn\'t go back and withdraw, you know, my literacy test after I had tried to take it. I wouldn\'t go back."', '"Back,Know,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"Why should I leave Ruleville, and why should I leave Mississippi? I go to the big city, and with the kind of education they give us in Mississippi, I got problems. I\'d wind up in a soup line there."', '"Education,City,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"I had to leave, and my husband was forced to stay on this plantation until after the harvest season was over. And then the man that we had worked for, he\'d taken the car, and the most of the few things we had had been stolen."', '"Car,Man,Harvest"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'If the white man gives you anything - just remember when he gets ready he will take it right back. We have to take for ourselves.', '"Man,Remember,White"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', 'They talked about how it was our rights as human beings to register and vote. I never knew we could vote before. Nobody ever told us.', '"Nobody,Never,Vote"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"One day, I know the struggle will change. There\'s got to be a change - not only for Mississippi, not only for the people in the United States, but people all over the world."', '"Change,Struggle,World"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd8', '"It was the 31st of August in 1962 that eighteen of us traveled twenty-six miles to the county courthouse in Indianola to try to register to become first-class citizens. We was met in Indianola by policemen, Highway Patrolmen, and they only allowed two of us in to take the literacy test at the time."', '"Time,Miles,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', '"Let the world know you as you are, not as you think you should be, because sooner or later, if you are posing, you will forget the pose, and then where are you?"', '"World,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'Wrong is for other people.', '"People,Wrong,Other"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', '"Being a funny person does an awful lot of things to you. You feel that you mustn\'t get serious with people. They don\'t expect it from you, and they don\'t want to see it. You\'re not entitled to be serious, you\'re a clown."', '"Funny,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'I never liked the men I loved and never loved the men I liked.', '"Men,Never,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'Affectation is a very good word when someone does not wish to confess to what he would none the less like to believe of himself.', '"Good,Believe,Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'Personal beauty is a greater recommendation than any letter of reference.', '"Beauty,Personal,Recommendation"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'Your audience gives you everything you need. They tell you. There is no director who can direct you like an audience.', '"Everything,Your,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcd9', 'Men always fall for frigid women because they put on the best show.', '"Best,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdb', 'Chords that were broken will vibrate once more.', '"Will,Broken,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdb', '"Can ye fathom the ocean, dark and deep, where the mighty waves and the grandeur sweep?"', '"Dark,Waves,Ocean"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdb', '"The angel of mercy, the child of love, together had flown to the realms above."', '"Love,Angel,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdc', 'I was a go-go dancer at the Dom on East 10th Street in NYC. This was a glittering ballroom over Stanley\'s Bar. 1965.', '"Street,Bar,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdc', '"If someone is alone reading my poems, I hope it would be like reading someone\'s notebook. A record. Of a place, beauty, difficulty. A familiar daily struggle."', '"Beauty,Alone,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdc', '"My novels are about a generation of Americans who lived between 1940 and 2000, who resisted the postwar political and cultural forces by choosing a wandering life of impoverishment and wonder. Inevitably, race and economics are a big part of their stories. Childhood, childishness, and children are never far."', '"Life,Childhood,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdc', '"I grew up reading 19th-century novels and late Victorian children\'s books, so I try for a good story full of coincidence and error, landscape and weather. However, the world was radically changed during my lifetime, and I tell of that battering as best I can."', '"Best,Good,Weather"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdc', '"In poetry, I have, since very young, loved poetry in translation. The Chinese, the French, the Russians, Italians, Indians and early Celts: the formality of the translator\'s voice, their measured breath and anxiety moves me as it lingers over the original."', '"Poetry,Me,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"The most intense curiosity and excitement prevailed, and though the weather was uncertain, enormous masses of densely packed people lined the road, shouting and waving hats and handkerchiefs as we flew by them."', '"Weather,Curiosity,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', 'Yet thousands of slaves throughout the southern states are thus handed over by the masters who own them to masters who do not; and it does not require much demonstration to prove that their estate is not always the more gracious.', '"Always,Own,Prove"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"The vast concourse of people who had assembled to witness the triumphant arrival of the successful travellers was of the lowest orders of mechanics and artisans, among whom great distress and a dangerous spirit of discontent with the government at that time prevailed."', '"Time,Great,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', 'In the north we could not hope to keep the worst and poorest servant for a single day in the wretched discomfort in which our negro servants are forced habitually to live.', '"Hope,Day,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"The white man\'s blood and bones have begotten this bronze race, and bequeathed to it in some degree qualities, tendencies, capabilities, such as are the inheritance of the highest order of human animals."', '"Man,White,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"A great number of the women are victims to falling of the womb and weakness in the spine; but these are necessary results of their laborious existence, and do not belong either to climate or constitution."', '"Women,Great,Falling"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"But I do not admit the comparison between your slaves and even the lowest class of European free labourers, for the former are allowed the exercise of no faculties but those which they enjoy in common with the brutes that perish."', '"Free,Exercise,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"I have been out again on the river, rowing. I find nothing new."', '"River,New,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"I have been taking my daily walk round the island, and visited the sugar mill and the threshing mill again."', '"Daily,Walk,Sugar"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"I have sometimes been haunted with the idea that it was an imperative duty, knowing what I know, and having seen what I have seen, to do all that lies in my power to show the dangers and the evils of this frightful institution."', '"Power,Duty,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"I said I thought female labour of the sort exacted from these slaves, and corporal chastisement such as they endure, must be abhorrent to any manly or humane man."', '"Man,Endure,Said"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', 'The master\'s irresponsible power has no such bound.', '"Power,Master,Irresponsible"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', '"Yesterday morning I amused myself with an exercise of a talent I once possessed, but have so neglected that my performance might almost be called an experiment. I cut out a dress for one of the women."', '"Women,Morning,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', 'Simplicity is a great element of good breeding.', '"Good,Great,Simplicity"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdd', 'I want to do everything in the world that can be done.', '"World,Done,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"God didn\'t give up on me. I am somebody in God\'s eyes... Let me be a prime example of how I\'ve been through the storm and the rain, and I made it over."', '"God,Rain,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"My lips are big, but my talent is bigger."', '"Talent,Big,Lips"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'Have a little faith. Don\'t give up.', '"Faith,Up,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'You can\'t go into something good until you let go of all the bad stuff because you\'ll find yourself steady bringing up all the old in a new situation.', '"Good,Yourself,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'True story - I had index cards; I would write things on them and post them on the mirror in the bathroom. And I would speak it. Because you have to speak life. You have to speak what you want. You have to watch what you say because it\'s power in your tongue.', '"Life,Power,Mirror"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'It\'s hard to be patient. It\'s hard to sit back and actually wait and allow everything - just let it be.', '"Wait,Back,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I always say you\'ve only got one life to live, and you\'re not promised a tomorrow. So, you might as well just have a good time with it."', '"Life,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"When I realized I was having trouble reading, I was too embarrassed to ask for help. Some teachers believed in me, but I just wasn\'t focused on school - I was into the music and trying to please my dad."', '"Music,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I like to play dress up, I\'m in love with fashion."', '"Love,Dress,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"When I\'m out on the stage, it gives me this rush and anything that\'s on my mind and everything I\'m going through is forgotten about."', '"Me,Mind,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'It\'s always good when you can bring two artists together who are totally different.', '"Good,Together,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I want to do all types of music, music for all people. I want my music to be encouraging, to help people."', '"Music,People,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I\'m very soulful. I grew up singing in church. When I sing a song, I like to feel what I\'m singing."', '"Song,Singing,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I\'ve been wanting to sing for a long time. I\'ve been singing all my life, and I\'ve tried different record companies, but it seemed like - it was such a struggle and so hard to get out there. So, I said, \'I\'m gonna go on American Idol and see how far it takes me.\'"', '"Life,Time,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I been through some things but I worked hard to get to where I\'m at.', '"Hard,Through,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I feel like a good mom. I\'m a strong woman now... Don\'t look down on me. Pray for me because I\'m trying.', '"Good,Mom,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I caught a lot of flak for being a young mama.', '"Mama,Young,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"\'Cause when I had my child, people tried to make me feel like life was over for me, and I started to believe that."', '"Life,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'You\'ve got to make it a good example for those kids regardless of how much you mess up.', '"Good,Mess,Good Example"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I want people to just to see, all you got to do is have a little faith."', '"Faith,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I seemed so different from other kids; I grew up in church and felt a connection with God, and a lot of kids my age really didn\'t understand that."', '"God,Age,Connection"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I wanted people to see me, to change their minds about me."', '"Change,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I want to still be singing at 70 years old. I want to be open to the dreams I haven\'t even dreamed up.', '"Dreams,Singing,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I\'ve never been in a competition before, and I said I\'m going to go. I think - I just love to sing."', '"Love,Competition,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I think my purpose was just to get out and sing. I love to sing. I wasn\'t even in it for the - you know, the prize. I was, like, \'Hey, man, I\'m going to sing.\'"', '"Love,Man,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I\'ve been singing in church since I was little; my grandmother is a pastor.', '"Singing,Church,Pastor"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I want real love.', '"Love,Real,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"When I was a child, I used to dream about being onstage in front of thousands of people, and it happened. It\'s not about the fame; it\'s about people being touched."', '"People,Fame,Child"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'You can\'t tell me that dreams don\'t come true. My life is proof that they do.', '"Life,Dreams,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I didn\'t want to be the type of mother where my child came to me, and I can\'t even help her with her homework."', '"Me,Help,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'I stopped going to church for awhile.', '"Church,Awhile,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I wanted to be like some of the other young ladies that were in my school. I used to get picked on in church. Nobody wants to hang out with me. I want to hang out with the cool girls, and I started to take the wrong turn and do things I knew wasn\'t right."', '"Cool,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I never started out as an R&B singer. I grew up on all types of music - jazz, rock, pop, country, folk - and I wanted to bring that to my stage."', '"Music,Jazz,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"R. Kelly is different - music is always going through his brain. I remember we\'d be having a conversation, and he\'d choose a word I said and write a whole song to it."', '"Music,Brain,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I was very insecure growing up, and even though I\'m not that girl anymore, I think that the passion, that not feeling pretty and being insecure, is where my soul came from. And from early childhood, I let it free onstage."', '"Passion,Childhood,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I wanted people to know that I\'ve been through the rain. I\'ve been broken into pieces; I had a daughter at such a young age. There were times people would say, \'That\'s it for her.\' But that didn\'t happen."', '"Age,Rain,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"People root for me in such a way that when they come to a show, the experience of not knowing what\'s about to happen is a great thing."', '"Experience,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"A lot of times, we get into relationships, and we go in, and we take our old ways. If we take that old baggage into something new, it will never work."', '"Work,New,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"My main thing is family first. This industry can get you so caught up that you\'re so busy chasing, wanting to be number one and wanting to be the richest that you lose sight of what life really is about."', '"Life,Family,Busy"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I\'m a true country Southern girl that has always been built around family, cookouts and gatherings and being together on the holidays, singing together and laughing together. So whenever God opened doors for me to be able to travel the world and sing and do all the great things that I\'ve done, I didn\'t want to lose that part so family first for me."', '"Family,God,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I always tell people, \'Stop coming to me and telling what people are saying about me.\' I don\'t care anymore. I always get the people that come to me and say, \'Girl, I just want to tell you... \' and I\'m like, \'Nope.\'"', '"Me,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"Everything in life is a fight. Everybody wants this microwavable life, and it doesn\'t work like that. I\'m here to say, \'See what I went through? Look at me now.\'"', '"Life,Work,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', 'Working out started as something mental. It was a way to release and let some things go.', '"Way,Go,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I love Pilates, yoga, and spinning."', '"Love,Spinning,Yoga"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcde', '"I work out every day, sometimes twice a day."', '"Work,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I just take things one day at a time. I\'m just thankful that I have my legs, my arms, my eyes."', '"Time,Thankful,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I hope I contribute something useful to the human family. That\'s my intention. And I hope that it\'s useful to people.', '"Family,Hope,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I heard Skip James, and it pierced me. It felt like punk rock to me, real and raw. It was just one guitar, so simple yet so much expression. I wanted to feel and express like that, to take the shortest path to get to an emotion."', '"Path,Guitar,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I like going out and looking at people, and they inspire me so much."', '"Me,Looking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Art and culture are the greatest weapons against hate agendas, entrenched ideologies, and power structures that harbor and promote the business of divisiveness."', '"Business,Art,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'The one thing I had pure in my life was creativity.', '"Life,My Life,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Live performance is everything. First of all, I have terrible stage fright. But beyond that, once the music starts, it\'s OK."', '"Music,Live,Performance"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Just keep being yourself. Keep being yourself, and people recognize it."', '"Yourself,People,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"My most revered hero is Robert Johnson. His lyrics are so consistent with rap: the danger, the boldness, the creativity."', '"Hero,Creativity,Boldness"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I love the power of music and artistry and feel a responsibility having a platform to preach good things.', '"Love,Good,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I always call myself a recovering narcissist. I lived my life thinking everything was about me.', '"Life,Myself,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'There\'s certain artists that are meant to have certain paths and go the way of the corporate world. And then there are artists who are artists.', '"World,Way,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"So-called leaders aren\'t doing anything, so it\'s become the job of artists like me. We have to get on the front lines and fight for the people who have love and tolerance in their hearts and want to live in a unified world."', '"Love,Fight,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I usually go to secondhand stores and find what I can. I like finding interesting things: vests, blazers. I tell the band, \'We got to look good when we\'re up there.\' I learned it from Miles Davis. I read about his suits in his biography. Suits mean you\'re getting paid, and I like the idea that he looked good in his suits."', '"Good,Look,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'Music is something that\'s so powerful and means so much to me.', '"Music,Me,Powerful"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I was raised on African music, Harry Belafonte, and the Boston Pops. Then I got a dose of soul and hip-hop. I related to it immediately."', '"Music,Soul,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I want to be an artist, not be in the business of making hit records. Once I figured that out, everything became clear."', '"Business,Everything,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'We gotta bring new ideas to the table and empower each other.', '"New,Ideas,New Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Growing up in the neighborhoods I did in Oakland, you don\'t know the Beatles, but I started learning their songs."', '"Learning,Know,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I had a dream, as young people have quite idealistic dreams and goals, of, \'I\'m going to go to Los Angeles, and I\'m going to become a star!\' I did get this huge record deal, and I recorded this music under Xavier. That didn\'t really work out."', '"Dreams,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I knew I was an exhibitionist. I came from a huge family. I found an emotional connection being on stage.', '"Family,Connection,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"What I decided was I\'d be happier not being in the confines of a corporate infrastructure producing music. That\'s when I was free, and it opened up the door to have a different personality and incarnations. That\'s really when I had success in my music life. I was able to license my music."', '"Life,Success,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Prince was a hero. He was the brother, the black man that was a little different. As a kid, you thought, \'Wow, he\'s different. If he can do it, I can do it.\' I read that he was self-taught, so I started teaching myself to play the piano."', '"Myself,Black,Hero"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I write songs. I perform. I play the guitar. I play the keyboard.', '"Guitar,Keyboard,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'That\'s always the time to quit - when you have nothing to say as an artist and creative person.', '"Time,Nothing,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"My dad was born in 1905, and the men from that period were real men. He prepared me for the world."', '"Men,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Jimmy Iovine signed me personally to a million-dollar contract, and I lost my identity for a long time. That system is so predicated on making a hit, or you\'re out of here."', '"Time,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"If I can\'t be honest with music, forget it."', '"Music,Forget,Honest"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Fantastic Negrito is a persona, an incarnation in my third phase."', '"Persona,Phase,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'My dad was a strict Muslim. He had a lot of rules.', '"Dad,Rules,He"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"As long as we have have predatory capitalism, we\'ll have guns because the gun industry loves to make money out of guns."', '"Money,Gun,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I hitchhiked to L.A. with $100 and a keyboard.', 'Keyboard', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I thought my story was over. But that was when I realised I finally had a story to tell - and it seems to remind people of their own story.', '"People,Own,Story"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I really loved the hardcore alternative vibe Prince had on \'Dirty Mind.\'', '"Mind,Dirty,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I think that was always my strength. I was never a great player, but I could write."', '"Strength,Great,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"\'The Duffler\' is a very familiar story, a story about someone having something and not appreciating it until it\'s gone, when it\'s too late."', '"Late,Too Late,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I like being photographed without glasses. I don\'t want to be pretentious.', '"Glasses,Want,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'That makes me very happy as a human being to know what I\'m doing is an inspiration to people.', '"Me,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I\'m not interested in re-creating the same blues I love so much. I\'m interested in pushing boundaries.', '"Love,Not Interested,Blues"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Doing a concert, I look at a room full of different people, and I see you\'ve got Muslims, you\'ve got Jews, you\'ve got Christians, you\'ve got gays, you\'ve got straights, you\'ve got blacks, you\'ve got whites. I think, \'How can I unite these people through song?\'"', '"Look,Song,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I came up with the album name \'Please Don\'t Be Dead\' because I felt like we\'d lost our way as a society - and I know what happens when you chase the wrong things. It\'s the story of my life.', '"Life,Society,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I fear for the lives of my daughters. I am uncertain about what kind of future they will face.', '"Future,Fear,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"\'Fantastic\' is self-explanatory, you know? And the \'Negrito\' is a way to open up blackness to everyone - you know, make it playful, international. It\'s extremely positive in my view; it\'s my affair with this music."', '"Positive,Music,View"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"The idea of \'raw\' music, to me, is honesty: getting people to feel you with the least amount of production possible, the shortest distance traveled emotionally, sonically."', '"Music,Honesty,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I take the purest and hardest forms of music... and come in completely fresh from a production standpoint. It\'s like hip-hop production, because there\'s a lot of taking the best parts and a lot of the repetitiveness."', '"Best,Music,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Nothing unifies people more than music, more than that universal riff. The one thing that unifies us and the hope that we can have, especially being an artist, is that we can create music that can build bridges and smash down very bad ideas."', '"Hope,Music,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I think once I had lived life, once I had failed enough in this lifetime and got back up a thousand times from failing, I really connected to the blues."', '"Life,Back,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I don\'t mind being the voice of the New Oakland to maintain the integrity and edge of it. Old Oakland and New Oakland is one and the same. It\'s connected. I aspire to be the bridge between both.', '"Integrity,Mind,Bridge"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Your dream can die. You will probably give up. But from there, you can start everything over."', '"Die,Start,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"My life, my failures. I hope that gives people the lesson to rebuild their own lives."', '"Life,Hope,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"What did winning a Grammy do for me? It made me want to get rid of my Grammy, pack it away, and never see it again. It made me not want to speak to anyone who wanted to speak about my Grammy."', '"Me,Winning,See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I wanted to do life, do something interesting. I ran out of things I wanted to say in my music, so I just put it down, sold all my gear, and put on some overalls and reconnected with the soil."', '"Life,Music,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I can\'t just sit back and write about the club when our democracy is under attack. I have to be a more positive force.', '"Positive,Democracy,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I throw up before every show. I\'m thinking about just making it part of the act.', '"Thinking,Act,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I think things happen, and we have no control over them, and what you take from them is really what is important."', '"Control,Important,Things Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'The streets spoke to me in a way that religion didn\'t.', '"Religion,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"\'Push back\' is the word; that\'s what we gotta do against ignorance. I see so much of it, and it\'s dangerous."', '"Ignorance,Back,See"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"It\'s amazing: when you are challenged with less, sometimes you can produce more."', '"Amazing,Sometimes,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"When I look into the audience, and I just know we understand each other, I can see their faces, and they know what I\'m talking about. I feel like I\'ve helped. Everything I\'ve been through in my life, it helps people. Then that makes it worth it."', '"Life,Look,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'Slaves and the descendants of slaves created world pop culture. Let\'s keep it real and be very respectful about that.', '"Culture,World,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Usually when tragedy is present, a great art movement is right behind it."', '"Art,Great,Tragedy"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '\'In the Pines\' is a very old song dating back to slavery. Lead Belly made it popular.', '"Dating,Song,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Ain\'t nobody more punk rock than Robert Johnson, Lead Belly, even Little Richard."', '"Nobody,Rock,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I\'m in a collective with the same guys I met on the streets at 12. The greatest investments I ever made were those friendships.', '"Same,Collective,Greatest"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"When I was born, my mother said all the nurses wanted to come see the colored baby."', '"See,Born,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Everybody agreed I had all this talent, but I didn\'t know what to make of it."', '"Talent,Know,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I became Fantastic Negrito, and I felt like there was a rawness and an honesty in that music that I could relate to. That I was ready, finally, in my life to be that honest with myself."', '"Life,Music,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Exercise is good for you, so I\'m always walking. I don\'t drink sodas or eat fast food, either."', '"Good,Food,Exercise"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'Blues purists may hate what I do sometimes because it\'s a little dirtier.', '"Hate,Sometimes,Blues"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I had this dream that you get this record deal, and you\'re a star, and everybody loves you - but I was a youngster, and it didn\'t work out that way."', '"Work,Way,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"When I was a youngster, I wrote all this music - it just came out of me - and I think record executives were like, \'Oh, wow, he\'s a genius, let\'s give him a million dollars!\' But the minute I started producing the records, they\'d be like, \'Oh, my God, you\'re terrible! You\'re all over the place! We can\'t market this!\'"', '"God,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"I could have worked with great people like Nile Rodgers, which I regret. I don\'t have many regrets, but I remember he\'d shown some interest, and I was just in my own world, man."', '"Great,Regret,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"There came a point where I did give up on music, but I\'m the kind of person that when I face obstacles, I become more determined. It\'s just something weird within me."', '"Music,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"Without busking, there is no Fantastic Negrito."', '"Without,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'NPR changed my life; I don\'t even front.', '"Life,My Life,Front"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I want to make other people around me smarter and more powerful.', '"Me,People,More"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', '"We should not fear what is new, but we should not throw out that which is in the past but is still valuable."', '"Fear,Past,New"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I think I was made for live music. It\'s just great.', '"Music,Great,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcdf', 'I try to be as positive a person as possible.', '"Positive,Person,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"My father Kamran Khan was a successful producer, director and actor in B-grade films."', '"Father,Actor,Producer"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"In \'Purab Aur Paschim,\' there\'s one of the nicer patriotic scenes which is patriotic without going jingoistic. There\'s a scene set in a rotating restaurant, where Pran, who has left India, is completely running India down and Manoj Kumar is taking up for India. And there\'s that song \'Jab Zero Diya.\'"', '"Restaurant,Song,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Everyone has flaws. We are only human after all. But what\'s important is, we don\'t let our flaws stand in the way of what we can achieve."', '"Flaws,Way,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'The stars that I\'ve worked with started their careers almost at the same time as me. Whether it is Shah Rukh Khan or Aamir Khan or Salman Khan.', '"Time,Stars,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I don\'t smoke, drink, do drugs or even have affairs. If I don\'t even swear, I should be put in a shrine and sanctified."', '"Smoke,Drink,Swear"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"One of my favourite scenes ever is in Mr India - when the kids are hungry and Sridevi comes with the pastries etc, and they become friends. It\'s impossible not to get teary-eyed."', '"Impossible,Hungry,Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"It is really a sad state of affairs if I am still the only commercially successful woman director. We need a lot more commercially viable women, not only in direction."', '"Sad,Women,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When I am making a movie, I am very casual; wearing chappals, and have my hair tied. However, when I am judging a show, I take care of myself and get the makeup and hair done."', '"Myself,I Am,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I feel 95 per cent of Indian boys are mama\'s boys and a few of them couldn\'t come out of their mother\'s shadows. Salman Khan is one of them. I feel one of the reasons he is unable to find a soul mate is he looks for his mother in every girl.', '"Soul,Feel,Mama"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I don\'t care for jewellery and fancy clothes.', '"Care,Clothes,dont Care"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'People don\'t wish to watch masala films of the \'50s any more. Audiences do not want loud films at all. They are watching Netflix and Amazon that have fresh ideas.', '"People,Ideas,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Shirin Farhad\' is a romantic tale of an unmarried couple who feel they can live together forever. Having crossed the marriageable age, what happens to them forms the crux of the story. The movie has several comic sequences with an emotional touch to it."', '"Age,Romantic,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I don\'t neglect my kids. They are my priority. They come on shoots.', '"Neglect,Come,Kids"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Whenever I visit abroad, people recognise me - it feels great."', '"Great,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Web series are the future.', '"Future,Web,Series"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"God bless IVF because it\'s never too late to conceive any more. However, having said that, I have to point out that going through IVF is a gruelling procedure; maybe that\'s why only a woman can go through it!"', '"God,Never Too Late,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Women directors in India have mostly made niche films. Naturally, those films have a limited market."', '"Women,Niche,Limited"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I always feel your movie will be as strong as your weakest link.', '"Feel,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Giving birth to triplets at the age of forty-three is no walk in the park, but I had little choice. I got married at the young age of forty, and both my husband, Shirish, and I were keen to start a family soon."', '"Family,Age,Walk"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I\'ve always been told that because of \'Main Hoon Na,\' a lot of female filmmakers have come up but I maintain that direction is a \'genderless\' job."', '"Direction,Always,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'IVF is a wonderful thing. One has to ignore the injections as the reality is that nobody is going to invent a pill that you can take to get a baby.', '"Reality,Nobody,Ignore"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"\'Main Hoon Na\' will always be special since it was my first film but in my subsequent films, I was trying to show off with gimmicks that didn\'t aid the narrative in any way."', '"Way,Will,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:37:00', '2023-05-29 11:37:00'),
	('389444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I see people every day who think they\'re the be all and end all of the industry. I\'ve seen so many people come and go, but the industry doesn\'t revolve around one person."', '"Day,People,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"The climax of \'Johny Mera Naa,\' it\'s one of the best climaxes ever written, ever directed. If I ever wanted to remake a movie, I\'d try to do this one, just for the climax."', '"Best,Try,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I was chosen over British and French choreographers to work on \'Bombay Dreams.\'', '"Dreams,Work,Chosen"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"It is an extremely difficult task to make an entertaining movie, which is completely aesthetic and you can watch again and again."', '"Difficult,Aesthetic,Task"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I make aesthetic movies which are grand and with some of the biggest stars. It\'s not fair to run them down. I don\'t make tacky films.', '"Movies,Stars,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Every person on Twitter is a critic. Every person who watches a movie will write a blog or a review. You can\'t go out trying to impress these people.', '"People,Will,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When I see a lot of the big Hollywood movies, I see they are all financed by Indian studios."', '"Movies,See,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Since \'Main Hoon Na\' is a cult film, if I want to make a sequel, the story has to be good!"', '"Good,Story,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Luckily, filmmaking is not a nine-to-five job."', '"Filmmaking,Job,Nine-To-Five"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I had babies at the age of 43 because sometimes you get so caught up, you are making your life, building your career and may be you don\'t want to get married."', '"Life,Age,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I make commercial films only. I don\'t make small, boring films."', '"Boring,Small,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I always say a film should be given breathing space.', '"Space,Always,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I never thought \'Mein Hoon Na\' will do so well in Pakistan. Whenever I meet Pakistanis in London or the U.S., they have so much love and affection for me because of \'Mein Hoon Na,\' which was my most criticised film in India."', '"Love,Me,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Cinema, art and culture should definitely be shared. These things transcend borders."', '"Art,Culture,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Personally, I love being a mother the most. I dream of taking holidays with my three kids. I want to take my kids to beaches, gardens, the farm, malls everywhere."', '"Love,Three,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Professionally, I like doing one thing at a time and enjoy directing the most."', '"Time,Doing,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I have to be someone; maybe I\'m just doing it for my father. When I made a movie, it had to be a hit because when he died, he was a flop director."', '"Father,Doing,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I\'m not promiscuous by nature.', '"Nature,Promiscuous"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'The idea of directing my own movie is definitely more challenging than choreography.', '"My Own,Own,More"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I had to let go of many things because we did not have much money growing up. Like joining the Film Institute in Pune or learning the piano.', '"Money,Learning,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"You are only part of the film industry if you are doing well, let me tell you. You will be invited to parties and flowers will reach you on your birthday. When you are not doing well, you are really an outcast."', '"Birthday,Me,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Somewhere my dad gave up. He was really so successful at his level that after a point he could not handle failure.', '"Failure,Dad,Somewhere"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Before I had my babies, I would tend to be self-absorbed, and worry about little things, but now I am a changed person."', '"I Am,Little Things,Worry"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'For me feminism is equality.', '"Equality,Me,Feminism"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Every person with a phone is a critic.', '"Person,Phone,Critic"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I always say that cinema reflects life, not the other way round."', '"Life,Cinema,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I\'d taken \'Om Shanti Om\' to Japan and they loved it because they just love the not holding back of emotions.', '"Love,Emotions,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I have fully retired as a choreographer. I do not have the patience now to make actors learn their steps. For me, that ship has sailed. I have enjoyed 22 years of it."', '"Patience,Me,Ship"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'The best moment in \'Masoom\' comes when the boy tells him that he knows he\'s his father.', '"Best,Moment,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Even with a big budget, you can make a niche film."', '"Big,Budget,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"My experience in Bollywood has been this: You work hard, you deliver, and nobody finds fault with you."', '"Work,Experience,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"You are punished only when you are not performing as per expectation, and not because you belong to a particular religion, caste, or creed. Here, you fail because your vision is not right or you have not worked hard. That\'s why I believe we have true democracy in the film industry. How I wish the rest of the country was like the industry!"', '"Religion,Vision,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Manmohan Desai\'s films pack a lot of joy and have a child-like quality and you can see the director is having fun, but my movies don\'t suspend disbelief that much. But it\'s good to be compared to Manmohan Desai. He was run down by critics in his time."', '"Time,Good,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I don\'t socialise. My social life is minus zero.', '"Life,Social,Zero"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I am not an actress.', '"I Am,Actress,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Later in life there should not be any regrets. Sometimes you have children too early and regret it, \'If I wouldn\'t have, my career would have been different\' and sometimes when you don\'t have, you miss that opportunity."', '"Life,Opportunity,Regret"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"The problem with people is that no matter how good you are at what you do, it\'s never enough for them. There will always be someone to point out some flaw. Someone will always find something lacking in you."', '"Good,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Even as one of the best choreographers in the country, I was criticised for a lot of things I have done in life."', '"Life,Best,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I am a hands-on mother, so I take long gaps between films."', '"Long,I Am,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I would love to make a sarcastic film; I am so sarcastic that even my kids are now getting used to my sarcasm. You see it a lot in British comedy because that\'s their sense of humour.', '"Love,I Am,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Adopting a pet is like taking the responsibility of a baby.', '"Pet,Responsibility,Baby"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I never imagined myself making these big movies and being married and having kids.', '"Movies,Myself,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I think it is important to enjoy your work.', '"Work,Important,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'People tend to take themselves too seriously.', '"People,Seriously,Take"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"You get paid what you deserve, according to the money that your movie generates. I get much more than a lot of male directors and I also get less than some. But I get paid what I deserve and what I ask for."', '"Money,Deserve,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I would never want to do a content-driven film with a box office life of Rs 20 crore.', '"Life,Never,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I would say that all my films have more content than a \'content-driven film.\' It is not easy to make such films.', '"Easy,More,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'You can only make the film that\'s in you.', '"Film,Only,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"We have music playing at home, day and night."', '"Home,Music,Night"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Aamir Khan in a sense, was my first teacher for filmmaking. He used to answer my doubts on the sets of \'Joh Jeeta Wahi Sikander.\'"', '"Teacher,Filmmaking,Answer"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Filmmaking is all about people management.', '"Filmmaking,People,Management"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'The most creative director I have worked with is Mani Ratnam.', '"Creative,Director,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When I became a choreographer, I was not assisting any choreographer. I was assisting the director Mansoor Ali Khan for \'Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar.\' I was the fourth assistant director."', '"Fourth,Director,Any"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I always say that I\'m a filmmaker, not a factory. I don\'t have to churn out films every six months."', '"Always,Say,Six"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"After \'Main Hoon Na,\' I got married; so I took some time off."', '"Time,After,Got"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'It takes two years to make a good film.', '"Good,Two,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I can take stress on myself but I don\'t like it when stress comes to my husband or children.', '"Myself,Children,Stress"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"Shah Rukh is always experimental with his role as an actor. He is the same actor who did a film like \'Kabhi Haan Kabhi Naa,\' \'Asoka,\' \'Chak De! India\' and \'Swades\' and other so-called commercially successful films."', '"Always,Film,He"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When I meet parents in my children\'s school, they say there aren\'t good films for kids to watch. I wonder about the lack of such films too. What do my kids watch?"', '"Good,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'One should be able to take the whole family along to watch a film.', '"Family,Film,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When I make a movie, I don\'t do any shows because the focus is completely on the film but when I take up a show, it\'s an absolute relief!"', '"Focus,Because,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I am happy judging shows and making films. It is a good thing to do a film and then take up a show, considering it also keeps your popularity alive."', '"Good,I Am Happy,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'It is more difficult to make film which does not have a big name. People start questioning the cast and the budget.', '"Difficult,People,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Parenting three children at the same time has helped me grow as a filmmaker. It taught me to be more empathetic and understand what people want from me.', '"Time,Parenting,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I will only do something if it has credibility for me, and that includes the films I make, the TV shows I judge and ad-campaigns I sign up for."', '"Me,Will,Judge"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I prefer doing work that projects me as a woman and a mother.', '"Work,Me,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"For the audience, actors carry out specific roles of men and women through the character that they play out on screen. The director on the other hand is not doing a gender-specific job. So, it is irrelevant if the person who makes a particular film is a man or a woman."', '"Women,Men,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"In \'Shirin Farhad\' I play the character of a Parsi woman. Though I was born a Parsi, in a Parsi family, I don\'t have the right accent."', '"Family,Character,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'Movie theatre gives a soulful experience.', '"Experience,Theatre,Soulful"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"When TV came, people said who will go to theatres to watch movies? When the Internet came, they said the same. And now it\'s the digital media... The doomsday predictions are always there but I don\'t think people will stop going to cinema halls because that is one experience you can\'t get at home."', '"Experience,Home,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I always wanted to make cinema which will entertain the masses, cinema that could be called escapist but is mounted on a realistic scale with high production values."', '"Cinema,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I don\'t think there is anything new left for me in choreography.', '"Me,New,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"A part of \'Happy New Year\' is inspired by western pop culture, the pop music videos of Michael Jackson, Madonna and Duran Duran in the \'80s."', '"Music,Culture,New"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I\'m happy directing films. On television, the direction takes your entire life away."', '"Life,Direction,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"At least in films you will go, you shoot for four to five months and then you can take a break. But I know how TV works... the directors are mindblowing, they work non-stop."', '"Work,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', '"I am not anti-men, I believe truly that we are meant to be equal. We should be judged equally and I think I am a living example of feminism."', '"Believe,I Am,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'There are two aspects around which the dynamics of Bollywood revolve - chivalry and chauvinism.', '"Two,Chivalry,Around"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce1', 'I like to entertain all kinds of audiences with my films.', '"Like,Entertain,Kinds"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', '"I grew up with \'Star Trek,\' so to get to do anything in it was fun for me."', '"Me,Fun,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', 'We are all quick to point out all the differences but not as willing to accept what bonds us as humans.', '"Differences,Accept,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', '"When I read a script, if I feel it\'s written with the idea of just bashing other people, then I shy away from it. Sometimes it\'s some guy coming out with his own hatred, and I don\'t need to be a part of it."', '"Feel,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', 'Does Hollywood do movies about terrorism? Yeah. And why do they do that? Because it sells.', '"Movies,Terrorism,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', '"When you play a character, you get to see the world through their eyes. Whether it\'s a fictional world or a real world, you do get to see somebody else\'s point of view, whether he\'s a good guy or a bad guy."', '"Good,Eyes,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', '"Sometimes stereotyping happens not because of any nefarious reasons but rather because people don\'t know who you are or where you come from, so they go for the broad strokes about you, your culture, your faith, all that."', '"Faith,Culture,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', 'The box office has become global. I think that factors in to the question of how to portray different ethnicities and cultures.', '"Global,Box,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce2', '"I think you can do science fiction, but you have to ground it in some realism. People need to identify with the characters, with their plights and their issues."', '"Science,People,Science Fiction"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The Berlin Wall wasn\'t the only barrier to fall after the collapse of the Soviet Union and the end of the Cold War. Traditional barriers to the flow of money, trade, people and ideas also fell."', '"War,Money,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Americans have so far put up with inequality because they felt they could change their status. They didn\'t mind others being rich, as long as they had a path to move up as well. The American Dream is all about social mobility in a sense - the idea that anyone can make it."', '"Change,Path,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"But as the arms-control scholar Thomas Schelling once noted, two things are very expensive in international life: promises when they succeed and threats when they fail."', '"Life,Succeed,Scholar"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The tallest building in the world is now in Dubai, the biggest factory in the world is in China, the largest oil refinery is in India, the largest investment fund in the world is in Abu Dhabi, the largest Ferris wheel in the world is in Singapore."', '"World,Dubai,Investment"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"During the Cold War, we were interested because we were scared that Russia and the United States were going to go to war. We were scared that Russia was going to take over the world. Every country became a battleground."', '"War,World,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The great drama of Russian history has been between its state and society. Put simply, Russia has always had too much state and not enough society."', '"History,Great,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The American dream seems to be thriving in Europe not at home.', '"Home,American Dream,American"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The American consumer, even today, the weight of the American consumer in the global economy is China plus India doubled. So, it\'s tough to replace that."', '"Today,Tough,American"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I think that liberals need to grow up.', '"Grow,Need,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"I very much want to be in the business of creating content, of doing stories all over the world rather than figuring out what the business model is for \'Newsweek\' on the iPad, although that\'s very important work as well."', '"Work,Business,World"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Whenever someone says the word community, I want to reach for an oxygen mask."', '"Community,Mask,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Conservatives used to believe in confronting hard truths, not succumbing to comforting fairy tales. Some still do."', '"Believe,Fairy,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"What we see today is an American economy that has boomed because of policies and developments of the 1950s and \'60s: the interstate-highway system, massive funding for science and technology, a public-education system that was the envy of the world and generous immigration policies."', '"Science,Technology,Today"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'Things happening around the world are affecting you and me.', '"Me,World,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"There is a huge crisis of employment in America, in the Western world in general."', '"World,America,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"It is absolutely clear that government plays a key role, as a catalyst, in promoting long-run growth."', '"Government,Growth,Key"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I should not be judged by a standard that\'s not applied to everyone else.', '"Everyone,Standard,Else"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The Web forces me to be disciplined and not to waste time - but before the Web was invented, there were plenty of opportunities to do that anyway."', '"Time,Me,Waste Time"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I\'m largely in favor of financial reform.', '"Financial,Favor,Reform"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"I am an American, not by accident of birth but by choice. I voted with my feet and became an American because I love this country and think it is exceptional."', '"Love,I Am,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"In the 1990s, we were certain that Saddam Hussein had a nuclear arsenal. In fact, his factories could barely make soap."', '"Soap,Make,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"If you go to India the roads are being built almost entirely with private sector money and by the private sector. If you look at many, many countries in Europe that\'s how they\'re doing it."', '"Money,Look,Roads"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I enjoy writing but I much prefer the experience of having written.', '"Experience,Enjoy,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"You know, when the cost of capital goes down, when credit becomes cheap, people start taking greater and greater risks."', '"Risks,People,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The Chinese economy\'s still not that much of a consumer economy.', '"Consumer,Still,Economy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'Politics and power is a realm of relative influence.', '"Politics,Power,Influence"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The technological revolution at home makes it much easier for computers to do our work.', '"Work,Home,Computers"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'Having your fiscal house in order and having a more manageable macro-economic future is going to be very useful in creating growth.', '"Future,Growth,House"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The one show that I will continue to be a guest on is \'The Daily Show\' with Jon Stewart, if he\'ll have me. It\'s not competitive with CNN and it\'s too much fun."', '"Daily,Me,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'My friends all say I\'m going to be Secretary of State. But I don\'t see how that would be much different from the job I have now.', '"See,Job,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'Alaska itself is an unusual state.', '"State,Alaska,Unusual"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'What happens in the media is the cult of personality. The brands who have been forced to cut their staff have been forced to take on the brands of journalists.', '"Personality,Media,Happens"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"If we didn\'t have the rest of the world growing, the United States economy would be in much worse shape than it is today."', '"Today,World,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'It\'s not possible for two countries to be the leading dominant political power at the same time.', '"Time,Power,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"In a world awash in debt, power shifts to creditors."', '"Power,World,Debt"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"America\'s growth historically has been fueled mostly by investment, education, productivity, innovation and immigration. The one thing that doesn\'t seem to have anything to do with America\'s growth rate is a brutal work schedule."', '"Education,Work,Growth"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"If there is one lesson for U.S. foreign policy from the past 10 years, it is surely that military intervention can seem simple but is in fact a complex affair with the potential for unintended consequences."', '"Simple,Past,Lesson"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I grew up in this world where everything seemed possible.', '"World,Everything,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'Culture follows power.', '"Power,Culture,Follows"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"If a senator calls me up and asks me what should we do in Iraq, I\'m happy to talk to him."', '"Me,Happy,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I\'d be kidding if I said that I predicted the financial collapse.', '"Financial,Said,Kidding"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Whenever societies do well, they believe that there is something in their cultural DNA that made it happen."', '"Believe,DNA,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"When you\'re failing, there\'s a very powerful incentive to put ideology aside and just do what seems to work."', '"Work,Ideology,Powerful"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'It hasn\'t been easy to find American citizens who are willing to pick fruit in 110 degree weather.', '"Weather,Fruit,American"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"One of the things that has been very difficult in Libya is the sense of uncertainty - the sense that they haven\'t actually finished the revolution, that there was still a great deal of uncertainty. That uncertainty has made Libya harder for business in terms of oil and other things as well."', '"Business,Great,Uncertainty"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The situation in Syria is quite different from Libya.', '"Situation,Quite,Different"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"In a very weak economy, when you say \'cut government spending,\' what you mean is you\'re laying off school teachers and you\'re de-funding various programs that put money into the economy. This means you have more unemployed people that then draw unemployment benefits and don\'t pay taxes."', '"Money,Government,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The markets are much more interested in America\'s long-term trajectory than they are in feeling that there is an acute short-term crisis.', '"America,Crisis,More"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"There is very strong historical data that suggests the way societies grow is by making large, long-term investments."', '"Grow,Way,Data"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The United States is going to be a rich country, it is going to be prosperous, but it is not going to be able to take the lead in the next phase of global economic development."', '"Rich,Country,Development"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I don\'t want to paint a picture of total gloom and doom.', '"Picture,Paint,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'One of the great dilemmas for America will be that American companies will do very well while American workers might not.', '"Great,America,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'The world is changing very profoundly.', '"World,Very,Changing"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I think it is quite untrue that it is standard journalistic practice to name the interviewer when quoting from an interview.', '"Practice,Name,Interview"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'American influence is not what it used to be.', '"Influence,American,Used"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', 'I grew up in Mumbai.', '"Up,Mumbai,Grew"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Iran is a country of 80 million people, educated and dynamic. It sits astride a crucial part of the world. It cannot be sanctioned and pressed down forever. It is the last great civilization to sit outside the global order."', '"Great,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"CNN is getting smarter, and you can feel it in the stories, you can feel it in the depth with which they\'re covered, the kinds of people in terms of guests who are brought on air, the way in which issues are discussed."', '"Way,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"The people who watch Fox are not going to watch CNN. You know, let\'s be honest."', '"People,Know,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce3', '"Street protests in Saudi Arabia might warm our hearts, but they could easily lead to $250 a barrel oil and a global recession."', '"Street,Oil,Lead"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I love ice cream and gulab jamuns.', '"Love,Ice Cream,Ice"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I am very fond of technology and like to keep pace with change.', '"Change,Technology,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"If you were to put me under one umbrella, call me a storyteller."', '"Me,Umbrella,Call"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Friendship brings in a lot of honesty and trust into any relationship, especially a marriage."', '"Friendship,Trust,Relationship"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"To me, \'Bhaag Milkha Bhaag\' is definitely a landmark. It has taught me so much."', '"Me,Much,Taught"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Fitness is about keeping yourself healthy. This is something you do for yourself and for your loved ones.', '"Fitness,Yourself,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Every director has a sensibility and style, and what works is his originality and conviction."', '"Style,Originality,Director"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'People want a certain amount of respect when they watch a film: it should be worth of their time.', '"Respect,Time,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Whether it is crimes against women, whether it\'s discrimination against women, whether it\'s just social bias against women - these things should be anomalies; they should not be the norm."', '"Women,Discrimination,Bias"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Indian food beats everything else, in my book. The kinds of cuisine our country offers is just amazing. Every single dish has a variation depending on what region you go to, and that excites me the most about Indian food."', '"Food,Amazing,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"There was a phase when I would just loaf around, doing nothing. It had put my mom under a lot of stress. I knew her stress stemmed from her love for me, yet I never paid attention to her feelings. When it finally hit me that my idleness was taking a toll on her, I was genuinely sad and depressed."', '"Love,Sad,Mom"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"In any case, I am not a great one to make plans for the future."', '"Future,Great,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"If you had a fabricated story coming out every two weeks or every month, it would affect you. You would be like, \'What\'s the problem with people?\' or \'Why can\'t they let me be?\' And that\'s the thought that comes into anyone\'s mind."', '"Me,Mind,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Being healthy is not just about building a body: it is a lifestyle that manifests itself in your general outlook. It makes you more positive and optimistic and increases your energy level.', '"Positive,Energy,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I love travelling, especially to Goa."', '"Love,Travelling,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Everyone has a Milkha Singh in them.', '"Everyone,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Difficulty does not deter me. In fact, I find challenges exciting."', '"Me,Challenges,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Most Hindi movies tend to dramatise events. They are very dialogue heavy. Characters don\'t speak like people normally do in real life.', '"Life,Movies,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I like to make films with characters that resemble real people, about societies that exist."', '"People,Real,Exist"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I feel nervous before performing in live concerts, but it does not last more than five minutes."', '"Feel,Live,Nervous"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"My sister Zoya and I have been exposed to the best of cinema of all kinds - Chinese, Japanese, Italian, etc."', '"Best,Cinema,Sister"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"It was interesting to write ad films and scripts for TV shows before I moved on to writing a feature film. That helped me grow as a writer, and I also found out how long I could sit in front of a computer and see something through."', '"Me,Long,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Nobody is immune to feeling depressed.', '"Nobody,Feeling,Immune"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Work does affect my personal life, as it consumes most of my time. It takes away a lot from my family time."', '"Life,Work,Family"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"As the director, you are the organiser who has to have all the answers. You are the person with maximum clarity."', '"Clarity,Person,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I think nothing can be taken for granted - be it the fact that you get to work with a certain kind of talent, certain kinds of budgets, or that the audience looks forward to your work."', '"Work,Talent,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Apart from the highs and lows of when your film releases, there\'s a strange, addictive quality that making a film has because of all that drama. There\'s so much that goes on, and we miss it when it\'s over."', '"Quality,Drama,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"It does not feel any different being directed by a first-timer as long as I am convinced that the director is passionate about the film he or she is making. If you get a sense of their vision for the film and their aesthetics of your performance, then it does not matter whether you work with a new or an experienced director."', '"Work,Vision,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"If you are a doctor or farmer, be sincere about your profession. If you can do what you do honestly, you will end up serving your country."', '"Doctor,Farmer,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Filmmaking, whatever the window dressing or the scale of a film may be, is eventually about telling a story."', '"Window,Filmmaking,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Being a parent to my daughters, son to my parents, and friends to many people, I would wish for a society that\'s fair to everyone, that\'s free of prejudice and as non-divisive as possible."', '"Society,Free,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'A break-up between couples is traumatic for everyone.', '"Everyone,Between,Couples"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I remember so clearly as a kid, my biggest problem in life was I used to never follow up on anything."', '"Life,Remember,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"When I take up a film, I always think of the effect it will have on my children when they see the film years later."', '"Children,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Cinema, I always felt, is a very powerful mass medium to translate ideas in an engaging way."', '"Cinema,Way,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Even within escapist cinema, if you find a good story to tell, it will do well."', '"Good,Cinema,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Everything I do is gauged under the shadow of \'Dil Chahta Hai.\' Even \'Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara\' and \'Rock On,\' which are very urban films. So I am always seen through that lens."', '"Shadow,I Am,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"As an actor, I am extremely fortunate to portray Milkha Singh on the big screen."', '"I Am,Big,Actor"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I think it is important to time yourself to make the right choices. It\'s not responsible to go ahead and say a \'yes\' or \'no\' on a whim.', '"Time,Yourself,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'When I made my debut as an actor in \'Rock On!\' I was confident to get in front of the camera.', '"Rock,Camera,Debut"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I am not trained to be a director or an actor. I have learnt everything by watching other people work and studying their work.', '"Work,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"You have to be grateful for what you have, but you\'re always pushing further."', '"Grateful,Always,Be Grateful"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"\'Deewar\' has been remade so many times, \'Trishul\' has been remade so many times. But \'Don\' - no one has gone into this area as often as they have gone into these other movies, and I think it fits into the modern sensibility of movie viewing quite well."', '"Movies,Well,Gone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '\'Dil Chahta Hai\' is not the first film about friendship. \'Lakshya\' is not the first film about war and coming of age.', '"Friendship,War,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I guess just enjoying what you do and always wanting more of that enjoyment, satisfaction, and putting something together creatively - that gives me a lot of happiness."', '"Happiness,Together,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"When you go to a film set, of course you\'re going to do your job, and you\'re excited about being there, but you somehow feel fatigued that you are just doing this day in and day out."', '"Day,Feel,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'From being in a film and shooting to just being in a studio with my guitar and musicians was a welcome change.', '"Change,Guitar,Welcome"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"It\'s only when a project or film doesn\'t work, that you think about what you could have done differently - whether you chose unwisely, or was there something in your application in that role, as an actor, as a director or as a producer, that you could have done better."', '"Work,Better,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Amitabh Bachchan was the coolest character in every movie.', '"Character,Every,Movie"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '\'Dil Chahta Hai\' was too raw. We only thought about the film. We never thought where the film was going to go. We wanted to make a film on our own terms.', '"Never,Own,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'The power with which you can create a character is tremendous and probably more satisfying than actually being the person.', '"Power,Character,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"When not working, my days are lazy."', '"Lazy,Days,Working"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I take a more holistic approach to fitness than trying to achieve a certain body to display.', '"Fitness,Body,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"If someone has behaved badly with a woman. and she hasn\'t spoken about it for ten, 20, or 30 years, it\'s her prerogative when she wants to speak."', '"Woman,Speak,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"If I don\'t work out, I lose weight instead of gaining it."', '"Work,Lose,Weight"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I like to stay within the zone of one character. It would disturb me to break away and go into an entirely different territory.', '"Character,Me,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I feel with \'Don 2\' I got an opportunity to do a very good action with the kind of pace that I would like an action film to have.', '"Good,Opportunity,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"The first time I re-discovered the joy of watching an action movie was when I saw \'Die Hard.\' It was a completely simple plot - a guy goes to meet his wife, and the building gets taken over by terrorists - but I was completely blown away. Great characters, and it moved along really fast."', '"Time,Great,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"To me \'Qurbani\' was a good action film - it was fast, had one plot, and moved along at a pace, and it didn\'t really divert attention."', '"Good,Me,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"To me, action has to come from the plot."', '"Me,Action,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I usually play volleyball three times a week.', '"Three,Week,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I think it is important to play a sport. Apart from the joy of it, it helps keep you fit."', '"Joy,Important,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"\'Lakshya\' is a different genre of movie. While \'Dil Chahta Hai\' could be categorised as a romantic comedy, this is a war drama."', '"War,Romantic,Drama"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '\'Haqeeqat\' was a good war drama.', '"War,Good,Drama"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"The Ladakhis, as a people, are quite laidback."', '"People,Quite"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"With \'Dil Chahta Hai\' being the first film and \'Lakshya\' being the second, what people can expect from Excel Entertainment as a company, and from me as a director, is just good, clean entertainment. And hopefully, some residue of an idea or thought that you can take home and mull over."', '"Good,Home,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I have been a fan of movies from a very young age, and somehow, the magic of that - every single time I hear something or read something that could be made into a wonderful film or something somebody is asking me to be a part of - that connects. It just makes me feel like I\'m going to be part of something magical again."', '"Time,Age,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I think if I had a choice, I\'d like to be in a film with De Niro."', '"Choice,Film,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"After \'Rock On!,\' when I started acting, and I sang in the film, people asked me, \'What was the need to sing in your film?\' and things like that. I really don\'t have an answer for it. In terms of what made me do it? It just felt like the right thing to do."', '"Me,The Right Thing,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"To hear someone talk about their life - you get to know the way their eyes moisten up, how big the smile is or how comfortable their body language is while talking to someone."', '"Smile,Life,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I was very focused when I wanted to make \'Dil Chahta Hai,\' though it was difficult for me to convince people that I know how to make films and I will be able to direct and put a film together."', '"Together,Me,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"The more time you have, you should dedicate it to do creative work."', '"Work,Time,More"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'It amazes me how much noise there is on a set while people are trying to focus and do their jobs. But there\'s some kind of order within that chaos.', '"Focus,Me,Chaos"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"When I watched Guru Dutt\'s films, they just blew my mind."', '"Mind,Guru,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I realised that I enjoyed direction while making \'DCH.\' The process of putting a film together and working with the cast and crew felt good.', '"Good,Together,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Film festivals are important, as they often provide an opportunity to look at a film from a fresh perspective."', '"Opportunity,Look,Perspective"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Whatever films I make, the mandate is that it should touch the audiences and engage them from the first scene."', '"Whatever,Touch,First"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Even when I was writing the script for \'Don,\' I suspected it could lead to a sequel."', '"Lead,Writing,Even"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I cannot imagine of making a film without Boman Irani.', '"Imagine,Film,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I\'m a bit of an extremist.', '"Bit,Extremist"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I wish I\'d got my driving license at 18, not 22. I also wish I had graduated earlier, even though I didn\'t finish college."', '"Wish,Finish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Every movie gets exactly what it deserves.', '"Every,Exactly What,Exactly"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I think if you believe in an idea, then you should put it out there and be as original to the thought as possible without worrying about the risk."', '"Believe,Possible,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I think, the world over, new ideas have come from young people. I\'m not saying it doesn\'t happen, but it is rare that new or radical ideas come from old people."', '"World,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'I think all kids are rebellious. It\'s a part of growing up.', '"Growing Up,Up,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I used to lie a lot as a child, which I now regret. I think it is much easier just to tell the truth."', '"Truth,Regret,Lie"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Definitely, I feel that there is a need for more female producers, directors, and writers."', '"Feel,More,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"As much as a man would like to believe that he understands women, there is simply that much that he can write from their point of view or really understand them."', '"Women,Man,View"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"There is a certain highlighting of issues, be it emotional, be it social, or simply an entertainment one: they can be written or directed by a woman differently, with a different voice. I feel that their voice needs to be given more stage and more space."', '"Space,Woman,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'It\'s amazing how much the human mind and body can do and achieve.', '"Amazing,Mind,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"For \'Rock On,\' we not only acted as rock musicians; we also went into the studio to record songs and jammed live to get the concert feel right."', '"Feel,Live,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'It\'s very important to enjoy whatever you do in life.', '"Life,Important,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'Music was something I had put aside to make movies. Somehow I earlier felt there was only so much creative energy allotted to your life and only that much time to pursue your creativity. But I was wrong.', '"Life,Time,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"For me, to consciously seek unpredictable roles would be dangerous."', '"Me,Unpredictable,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"Every time you work with a new co-star, a whole new dynamic emerges."', '"Work,Time,New"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '\'BMB\' has opened up a world of possibilities. It has inspired me to believe that the really difficult things in life can be achieved by sheer application.', '"Life,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"As an actor, you buy into someone else\'s dream and make it your own, and you don\'t lose sight of that."', '"Lose,Own,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I basically like a bit more control. Even in my personal life, I need things to be done on time. If it\'s not done, I get impatient."', '"Life,Time,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', '"I was a complete vagabond till the age of 20, when I got my first job as an assistant director with Pankaj Parashar."', '"Age,Job,First"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce4', 'One fear setting on filmmakers is that the audience no longer has any patience. They want things to constantly move.', '"Patience,Fear,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce6', '"We\'re under some gross misconception that we\'re a good species, going somewhere important, and that at the last minute we\'ll correct our errors and God will smile on us. It\'s delusion."', '"Smile,God,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce6', '"Without a function, we cease to be. So, I will write till I die."', '"Die,Will,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce6', '"I write better in Cape Breton... too many people around in Ontario. Down there I meet all sorts of non-human people, but they don\'t bother me, and I don\'t feel I have to apologize on behalf of my species quite so often."', '"Me,Better,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce6', '"I write every day. I\'m always in the process of writing my last book, until the next one."', '"Day,Process,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce7', '"The first time I went to Iraq was October 2002, when Saddam was still in power, and then, subsequently, in January of 2003, about three-and-a-half months before the U.S. invasion. So, I got to see the before and after of Iraq, basically, before and after the war."', '"War,Time,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce7', '"Almost immediately, I remember right when Tikrit even fell, a few days after Baghdad fell, there was talks of insurgency, there was talks of jihad and of resisting the American occupiers, and slowly this turned into an organized movement."', '"Remember,American,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce7', '"I have lucky boots for military embeds, a lucky scarf for road trips, a lucky handbag, and lucky days of the week. I tap into my gut for \'right\' or \'wrong\' feelings about such simple things as whether I should go grocery shopping."', '"Simple,Feelings,Shopping"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce7', '"I had several near death experiences or very, you know, close calls, if you may, in Iraq. You know, there was an incident where I was nearly kidnapped."', '"Death,Know,May"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce8', '"I should learn the language of a politician - give away as little and keep the rest to yourself. Not lie, I just want to be more guarded."', '"Yourself,Lie,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce8', '"I can\'t hide things from my Maker, so it is better to be honest."', '"Better,Hide,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce8', '"I trust people too much, and the other tragedy is I can\'t say no."', '"Trust,People,Tragedy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce8', 'I want to become foreign minister of India one day and then President of India.', '"Day,One Day,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I\'m anything but a small-town girl. I have big, big dreams, and I plan on making them happen."', '"Dreams,Big,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I\'m blessed with good genes, but I also love to look my best self."', '"Love,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I hope that others can turn their negative thoughts into positive thoughts and improve their own lives.', '"Positive,Hope,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'There\'s bigger things to worry about than makeup.', '"Worry,Makeup,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I can\'t speak for everyone, but I know that I definitely don\'t want to be a consistent plastic surgery, cosmetic kind of scenario. I don\'t like going to the hospital. I don\'t want to put myself through pain. So I\'m very limited; I know what I need, and then I call it a day."', '"Myself,Pain,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I definitely am done with as much drama as I can be done with. I don\'t think it helps me with any of my business endeavors or the things that I\'m excited about.', '"Business,Me,Drama"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I\'m very proud, and God\'s blessed me with an amazing career."', '"God,Amazing,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"Women should have equal rights to men, every day."', '"Women,Men,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'There\'s no reason to hide anything; there\'s just timeliness of age and what\'s appropriate.', '"Age,Hide,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I get really upset when I\'m around liars.', '"Upset,Get,Around"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"Oh, I definitely feel that women are equal to men. No doubt about that."', '"Women,Men,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'m pretty feminine.', '"Pretty,Feminine"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'m just pretty proud of myself.', '"Myself,Proud,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I guess I\'m a passionate person.', '"Person,Guess,Passionate"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I think Trump\'s gonna be a great president. And Hillary\'s a great woman too.', '"Great,Woman,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'m a business person.', '"Business,Person,Business Person"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'m really not into black guys. I think that\'s more of a Kardashian thing. God bless them.', '"God,Black,More"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'It is incredible how important doctors are to our society and how they help individuals live up to their full potential in life. I hope to inspire and help others fulfill their best selves as I do my best to become the top doctor in the nation in my future.', '"Life,Best,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I have a lot of passion and experience with aesthetic surgery and look forward to helping men and women all over the world.', '"Experience,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I was assaulted twice by Aisleyne Horgan Wallace and Janice Dickinson.', '"Twice,Assaulted,Wallace"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I\'ll just let people think what they would like to think, and that\'s fine, because it really doesn\'t infringe upon my life."', '"Life,My Life,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I definitely have my own brand, and so I never, ever envision myself with anyone else\'s lips."', '"Myself,Never,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I think I\'m pretty confident, and I know I\'m different than everyone else, so I\'m going to do what\'s me."', '"Me,Know,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"My grandma was a nurse, and she helped a lot of transgender clients, so growing up, I was very aware of that, and my family and I have always been very supportive of people going through this."', '"Family,People,Transgender"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"When your kids are 5 or 6, they already start playing with makeup. And I was the only mother in freakin\' elementary school getting called in to deal with makeup on her daughter."', '"Start,School,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'A lot of people are liars who I work with; that\'s a shame.', '"Work,People,Shame"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I think some people are mentally unstable, and I don\'t think I should be around them."', '"People,Some People,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'Some people don\'t have the right surroundings to help get them through an experimental time or a tough time.', '"Time,Tough,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"If my daughter says she doesn\'t like something, I don\'t do it. It\'s up to Sophia."', '"Daughter,She,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'m just about social justice. Amen to women like me!', '"Women,Justice,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I\'ve hated my nose since I was 13.', '"Nose,Since,Hated"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"Even though I\'m already successful and have a career, it is always good to have your eggs in more than one basket."', '"Good,Always,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I think my daughter looks beautiful regardless if she\'s losing her baby teeth or if she\'s having a bad hair day.', '"Beautiful,Day,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I really embrace everything about my daughter.', '"Daughter,Everything,Embrace"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', 'I think there\'s different parenting styles.', '"Parenting,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"Not everyone\'s a perfect parent, but we do learn, and we grow from that. I\'m not trying to be harsh on my family because it does make them sad to think back about how they used to be and some of their choices."', '"Family,Sad,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
