	('389740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"A lot of my girlfriends are on Snapchat, and they were being scandalous with what they were showing on there. I keep it pretty simple. I give updates and share things."', '"Simple,Things,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
