	('389749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"My daughter knows she is loved. My daughter knows she has a mom, and I\'m there, and I\'m not worried about anything of what everyone else is worried about."', '"Mom,Daughter,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
