	('389780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fce9', '"I\'m actually a pretty upfront, honest person; if there\'s anything, I just confront it."', '"Person,Anything,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
