	('389790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcea', '"God gave women intuition and femininity. Used properly, the combination easily jumbles the brain of any man I\'ve ever met."', '"God,Women,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
