	('389792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcea', '"I find that, for me, personally - and this is in everyday life - if I\'m not growing, if I can\'t be stimulated in a conversation, then I am bored. And I\'m not good when I\'m bored."', '"Life,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
