	('389794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcea', '"In the face of excruciating pain and uncertainty, I never lost hope, and it never occurred to me to stop fighting - not ever."', '"Hope,Pain,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcea', '"It\'s still going on. I guess it will be until Redmond quits, dies or is jailed."', '"Will,Guess,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
