	('389828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"The \'hood don\'t really wanna hear it, but you need brown rice, you need wheat bread, stuff like that."', '"Hood,Bread,Rice"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I\'m not just a rapper. I\'m a child educator.', '"Child,Just,Educator"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"As long as you get your education and you stay focused, you can do anything."', '"Education,Long,Stay Focused"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I used to watch Oprah Winfrey, and whenever she used to lose weight, I used to be like, \'How\'s she losing it? What is she doing?\' But it\'s all about education and knowledge, feeding yourself and knowing that too much carbs is what gets us fat."', '"Education,Knowledge,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'It feels like Gangstarr is the purest group in hip-hop. They was shooting videos on the beach in the winter when the water was ice. Razor-blade music.', '"Music,Water,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'There\'s nothing I really believe about 50 Cent.', '"Believe,Nothing,About"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Fat Joe is signed to Fat Joe. I have a distribution deal for my label. I\'m independent. I\'m very happy with that.', '"Fat,Independent,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"There\'s two systems of health care: the one for the rich that\'s really good, then there\'s the one for the inner city, where they leave ladies in the emergency room unattended for 24 hours until they drop dead."', '"Health,Good,City"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I love owning my masters.', '"Love,Owning,Masters"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"When I introduce you to somebody, his name is Big Pun. When I introduce you to somebody, his name is DJ Khaled. When I introduce you to an artist, her name is Remy Ma. If I introduce you to somebody, it\'s Cool and Dre or Scott Storch - people who change the face of the game."', '"Cool,Change,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Fat Joe ain\'t out here trying to battle-rap everybody in the world. That\'s not what I\'m about.', '"World,Fat,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Mike Bibby\'s my brother.', '"Brother,Mike"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'The biggest killer of people is food.', '"Food,People,Killer"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I\'m trying to get in where I fit in and take it to the next level.', '"Trying,Next,Level"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I make hits.', '"Make,Hits"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"We go after legacies because we just know that, sooner or later, people will understand what we bring to this culture and bring to the game."', '"Culture,Game,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I would bump A Tribe Called Quest in my car all day.', '"Car,Day,Tribe"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"The hip hop industry is most likely owned by gays. I happen to think there\'s a gay mafia in hip hop. Not rappers - the editorial presidents of magazines, the PDs at radio stations, the people who give you awards at award shows."', '"Award,Gay,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"If I could gain 1,000 pounds and be healthy, I would love to do that."', '"Love,Gain,Healthy"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I beefed with 50 Cent for seven years.', '"Seven,Years,50 Cent"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"We\'re just trying to make \'The Darkside\' its own brand. It\'s Fat Joe, but it\'s \'The Darkside.\' We come with \'Vol. 2,\' make it crazier than \'Vol. 1.\' By the time \'Vol. 3\' come, we got a problem on our hands."', '"Time,Fat,Hands"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"There isn\'t a country I ain\'t touch in Africa. I just came back from South of France, I toured China, Japan, wherever you name, 60,000 people come out to see Fat Joe."', '"Fat,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I was really from the streets, and I really did hustle in a major way. When I got my record deal, I left the streets alone as far as hustling. I never, ever hustled again. I said, \'I\'m gonna change my life, I\'m going legit. This is where I\'m at.\'"', '"Life,Alone,Change"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I think I\'ll die underrated, but it\'s alright, man."', '"Man,Die,Underrated"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"As U.S. citizens, Puerto Rico has paid their part."', '"Puerto Rico,Paid,Citizens"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Food is like a legal drug. You can take 50 cents and walk into the store and buy a Twinkie and get high. And it\'s killing people.', '"Food,Legal,Walk"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I love Lil Wayne; that\'s like my little brother. He\'s just the coolest dude on Earth.', '"Love,Earth,Brother"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I have been Fat Joe since I was a kid. It\'s always been my name and always will be.', '"Fat,Will,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I never lose touch. If you let me tell it, I\'ll tell you I never got my just due and my respect for being one of the greats in hip-hop, and because of that, the fire never burned out. There\'s more and more of a need for me to succeed or take the legacy a step further, and that\'s what it is."', '"Respect,Fire,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I was at a party New Year\'s Eve, and - no lie - at least 10 different people came up to me. One guy was like, \'I lost 30 pounds because of you.\' So people just coming up to me. I don\'t know these people - random people."', '"Me,Random,Lie"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"See, me, I don\'t run away. During my successes or my failures, I put it on me."', '"Me,See,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Pun was just a natural-born genius with music, and he basically taught me so many tricks on how to make better music, even though I was the one that discovered him. He was so far advanced than me; he taught me a lot."', '"Music,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"We\'re in the same ghettos, same inner cities, and we\'re suffering from the same problems. Every problem the blacks have, the Latinos have."', '"Suffering,Problems,Problem"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I\'m known to be hands on 100%. I don\'t know any other way to be than a leader by example.', '"Way,Hands,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"What I do like about Donald Trump is that he\'s not bought by the lobbyists. He put up his own money, funded his own campaign. That means he\'s nobody\'s puppet."', '"Money,Nobody,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Being that I always perform, I started working out with a trainer to get that endurance and stamina. Now, I guess you could call me a gym rat."', '"Me,Endurance,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I don\'t think the Republicans care much about minorities.', '"Care,Think,About"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Who you know, 10 albums later, get better than he\'s ever been before? It\'s hard. To come from all this huge success like a \'What\'s Love,\' and a \'Lean Back,\' then take it back to the street with \'The Darkside.\'"', '"Love,Success,Street"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I make hit records. I make hit records to motivate the people.', '"People,Hit,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"We took Big Pun, a 700-lb Spanish guy, one of the greatest rappers ever, and made him a sex symbol. Women would wait on line to kiss him."', '"Women,Sex,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"For artists, the majority of the money we make comes from us being on the road and touring."', '"Money,Road,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I think I weighed about 450/460 at my heaviest. That\'s huge! That\'s Fat Joe. And you know, I always took pride in being fat."', '"Pride,Fat,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"After the success of my first album and the success of \'Flow Joe\' kind of faded, I was struggling to make some money and make ends meet."', '"Success,Money,Meet"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'The biggest misconception in the hip-hop industry is that people are only focused on the money. We should just be happy for everybody that is working in the hip-hop culture.', '"Money,Culture,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Your man Daddy Yankee, some black and white people who know what\'s going on in the \'hood and the clubs are supporting him and loving him. But he\'s speaking Spanish, and he\'s speaking directly to the Latino people, and the people who know the language really dig it."', '"Black And White,Black,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'It\'s hard to have a boom-bap hip hop record that goes No. 1 in the country.', '"Country,Hard,Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Man I got so many regrets. The biggest is that Eminem gave me so many demos - six different times he approached me, and I didn\'t sign him. Shame on me."', '"Man,Me,Shame"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Every ghetto you go to, Latinos and blacks are the two people that are together. We don\'t look at each other in any different way, like \'He\'s black; I\'m Latino.\' I look at us as one."', '"Black,Together,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I collaborate with Tidal because they\'re for the artists - the up and coming artists and the O.G.s in the game. It\'s like a home, the only place we have for the artists to find support."', '"Home,Game,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"If you gay, you gay. Like, that\'s your preference, you know?"', '"Gay,Know,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I would love to coach. I\'m not saying I\'m qualified to do it in the N.B.A., but I would love to try."', '"Love,Try,Saying"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"When I came up in hip hop, there was no such thing as a Puerto Rican rapper doing hip hop for many mainstream people, so I was the ship, the captain, and the crew."', '"People,Captain,Ship"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I realized, at a certain point, all my big people were dying. I couldn\'t see a clearer picture: what\'s the difference between me and him, of me being in a casket?"', '"Me,Picture,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"There\'s no such thing as too much. If there\'s too much, then that\'s a great thing."', '"Great,Too Much,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Latinos finally have a genre of music that represents them, and they\'re supporting reggaeton in such huge numbers that people can\'t help but notice there\'s a revolution going on."', '"Music,People,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"There\'s millions of gay people in the world. In 2011, you\'ve got to hide that you\'re gay? Like, you know what I\'m saying? Like, be real."', '"World,Gay,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Donald Trump, you already know. We can\'t have that guy in office."', '"Know,Guy,Donald Trump"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '\'Envy\' was a bit of a challenge for me. It was smooth.', '"Me,Envy,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"All I know is stars and hits, you know what I mean? I don\'t just sign a guy because he has a hot record. I sign a guy because he\'s a star. He\'s a pillar of the community."', '"Stars,Community,Hot"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Culturally, the arts of Puerto Rico is really unmatched by any other island."', '"Puerto Rico,Island,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"When I first started, I thought I was wack. Lyrically, I thought I was wack. The thing I had over everybody was that I was the realest rapper."', '"First,Over,Thought"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I stay around the young boys in the studio; I want to learn from them, and at the same time, I have a lot to offer them."', '"Time,Young,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Everything has to evolve. Music has to go somewhere. That\'s what keeps it fresh.', '"Music,Everything,Fresh"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"As a little kid, I watched hip hop get created. So it\'s an honour for me to represent the Bronx, the motherland of hip hop."', '"Me,Motherland,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"If you really analyze my music, there is a lot of violence in my music because the Bronx, at the era and time I was coming up, was almost equivalent to how a \'Braveheart\' or \'Gladiator\' movie would be."', '"Time,Music,Violence"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Chances are if I am the one to cosign people, they will become a big part of the industry."', '"I Am,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Once you achieve a level of success... you learn, something tells you, \'Man this ain\'t even for you.\' You got to share with the people. You got to inspire the people."', '"Success,Man,People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Talking to people from the heart matters, and it\'s unfortunately something brands have forgotten about. Celebrity endorsement deals try to gain recognition for brands, but at their core, what matters is if the celebrity truly backs the brand."', '"Heart,People,Celebrity"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I ain\'t here to tell nobody what\'s right or what\'s wrong.', '"Nobody,Wrong,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Mister Cee\'s a legend, man."', '"Man,Legend,Mister"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I come from nothing, and growing up, I really didn\'t have many people to inspire me, at least no good people to inspire me."', '"Good,Me,Good People"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Allen Iverson was the Tupac of basketball; he was a true revolutionary.', '"True,He,Basketball"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"J. R. Smith\'s incredible, man, just incredible off the bench."', '"Man,Bench,Incredible"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I\'ve failed once or twice real big, independent."', '"Real,Independent,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'MTV shows me love.', '"Love,Me,MTV"', '2023-05-29 11:38:00', '2023-05-29 11:38:00'),
	('389903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I\'m a huge fan of the Clintons. I love Hillary; I love Bill.', '"Love,Fan,Huge Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I ain\'t no Kennedy, I ain\'t no Diddy Combs, I ain\'t no Jay Z, I ain\'t got it like them."', '"Like,Got,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I\'m just a human being. I\'m from the projects, too."', '"Human,Human Being,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'It feels as if I never get my just due.', '"Never,Just,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Whenever I come out with a hit record, they\'ll say, \'Ah, that\'s because of R. Kelly. Oh, it\'s because of Ashanti. Oh, he\'s lucky.\'"', '"Because,Lucky,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I could battle rap forever, but it\'s a joke to me."', '"Me,Battle,Forever"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Minorities have been hustling backwards from check to check.', '"Check,Backwards,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I love the quality of TIDAL. I appreciate what they\'re trying to do and what they\'re trying to accomplish.', '"Love,Quality,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Biggie has been the logo for success, the logo for doing it big - from popping champagne, the ladies, the fashion."', '"Success,Doing,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"During my successes or my failures, I put it on me."', '"Me,Failures,Successes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I was scared to fly for a long time.', '"Time,Fly,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Latinos been a part of hip-hop culture and every other culture; we\'ve been influential in every aspect of life.', '"Life,Culture,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"We gotta be proud to be Latino. It\'s almost like we cheating because we\'re American and we live by American customs, but at the same time, we got that Latino culture. We cheating; we double dipping."', '"Time,Culture,Cheating"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"If you look at history, at the first time hip-hop was invented, there was a Latino right there. How they got erased, I don\'t know how that all came about."', '"History,Time,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"Any time Khaled comes to your video, it just steps it up that much more. He\'s so fun; people love him."', '"Love,Time,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"KRS One and LL Cool J are the biggest influences in my rap career, along with Heavy D."', '"Cool,Along,Rap"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I grew up pretty much with nothing.', '"Nothing,Pretty,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'Nobody in my family before me ever had anything.', '"Family,Me,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I always loved being fat, obviously. I\'m Fat Joe."', '"Fat,Always,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"This world is too hard for me to leave my kids, without me supervising and being there for them."', '"Me,World,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'All rappers exaggerate.', '"Rappers,Exaggerate"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"My parents are overweight, and I think the biggest problem we have in America is a lack of education. The place to start is with parents and teaching them to cook healthier."', '"Education,America,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'I wish we had more diversity.', '"Diversity,Wish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"It feels like we all win when Joe wins. People know the struggle, everything I had to overcome. People feel like that\'s them winning. If Joe could do it, they could do it."', '"Struggle,Winning,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"I\'m trying to work, be diverse and multi-talented."', '"Work,Trying,Diverse"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"When it\'s all said and done, I want to look back on my career and say I did numerous things."', '"Look,Done,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', 'The formula for a hit is saying what people want to hear.', '"People,Saying,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fceb', '"My coldest days, my darkest days, ain\'t no sun out, all I got is my fans. They the only people I ride for. Believe it or not, if you\'re a real Fat Joe fan, a Terror Squad fan, I do it for ya\'ll."', '"Believe,Ride,Sun"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Morocco is such a beautiful place. It\'s incredibly beautiful. And also it is captivating place because for a writer, you feel that you make impact. I mean, when I write something in the press, the day after in the fish market, people will be discussing it."', '"Beautiful,Fish,Beautiful Place"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"In the 1920s, big names in the Arab world spoke of Scheherazade as an example for intellectuals fighting for their rights. She was a fighter for the right of free expression."', '"World,Fighting,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Women are builders of civil society. We are the ones who are going to build it. You know why? We have no choice. Either you shut up, and you are humiliated, or you do what I\'m doing. You scream."', '"Women,Society,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"I go to the hamam and put henna on my skin and hair. Even when I go to New York, I let the shower run hot to create a steam hamam at my hotel. But when I finish with the bath, I put on expensive French creams."', '"Hot,Hotel,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"In Islamic societies, politicians can manipulate almost everything. But thus far, no fundamentalist leader has been able to convince his supporters to renounce Islam\'s central virtue - the principle of strict equality between human beings, regardless of sex, race, or creed."', '"Equality,Sex,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'Consumerist ads brainwash us into individualist and egotistic self-love.', '"Us,Self-Love,Ads"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"One cannot understand what\'s happening to women in the Middle East if they don\'t realize that the mothers are a strong, progressive force. The mothers push the daughters to get out of the harem, to get the education, to achieve what they could not even dream of."', '"Education,Women,Achieve"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"The woman with dark hair, wide hips, and a few extra pounds has always been the essence of beauty in Morocco."', '"Beauty,Woman,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'The Taliban is the Muslim version of the Salem witch trials.', '"Trials,Version,Muslim"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"A woman can walk miles without making one single step forward. As a child born in a harem, I instinctively knew that to live is to open closed doors. To live is to look outside. To live is to step out. Life is trespassing."', '"Life,Walk,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'Sharia law does not exist in the Koran. It was created by man.', '"Man,Law,Exist"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"You find in the Koran hundreds of verses to support women\'s rights, and perhaps four or five that do not."', '"Women,Support,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"The modern Muslim state has never presented itself as secular. Muslim nationalist forces, trapped by a militant and colonialist West unable to share or export its humanism, were driven to build up a rampart, to entrench themselves within the past."', '"Past,Never,Build"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'The waves of religion based on terrorism in the 1990s are based on the tormented response of a mutilated Muslim society whose progressive forces have been savagely emasculated. Why on earth is the Arab world so hostile to women? Why can it not see women as a force for development?', '"Women,Society,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"If women\'s rights are a problem for some modern Muslim men, it is neither because of the Quran nor the Prophet, nor the Islamic tradition, but simply because those rights conflict with the interests of a male elite."', '"Women,Men,Conflict"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Since all power from the seventh century on was only legitimated by religion, political forces and economic interests pushed for the fabrication of false traditions."', '"Power,Religion,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"The Western man declares that in order to be beautiful, a woman must look 14 years old. If she dares to look 50, or worse, 60, she is beyond the pale. By putting the spotlight on the female child and framing her as the ideal of beauty, he condemns the mature woman to invisibility."', '"Beauty,Beautiful,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"If there is one thing that the women and men of the late 20th century who have an awareness and enjoyment of history can be sure of, it is that Islam was not sent from Heaven to foster egotism and mediocrity."', '"History,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Someone else is going to read for me or go at my place to the mosque, and/or to tell me you shouldn\'t take anything from the West because the West is the enemy and so on. It is to me to decide. I am intelligent enough to be critical towards the West and take what I need and reject what is bad for me."', '"Me,I Am,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"There has been a terrible hemorrhage of educated women to the West where they can flourish. I understand, but it is terrible. We must stay home."', '"Women,Home,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"So much of Islam is Judeo-Christianity. It\'s impossible to divorce them. Islam is 600 years after Christ. Thousands of years after Judaism. Christ, Moses, Abraham - they are all in the Koran."', '"Impossible,Islam,After"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'Educated women armed with computers have defeated extremists by denying them a monopoly to define cultural identity and interpret religious texts. No extremist can say that women are inferior to men without being made a laughingstock on Al Jazeera. Islam insisted on equality between everyone.', '"Women,Men,Equality"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"There, they tell me to wear the veil. Here, they are telling me to put my hips in a little girl\'s skirt, and I am this lovely full woman. You\'ve got this Ph.D. and you\'re worrying, \'Am I skinny enough?\'"', '"Me,I Am,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', 'No man could have accepted me because I am too rebellious. It would have been catastrophe. I am too into my own thing.', '"Man,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"In Morocco, for a woman to earn her own living is the essential concern."', '"Woman,Living,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Growing up, I was taught that a woman should lower her gaze so that men could never know her thoughts. The so-called modesty of Arab women is, in fact, a war tactic."', '"War,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Contrary to what many Westerners believe, Islam has a rich tradition of secular painting in spite of its ban on images. It is only in religious rituals that the use of pictorial representation is totally prohibited."', '"Believe,Painting,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"While Muslim men describe themselves as insecure in their harems, real or imagined, Westerners describe themselves as self-assured heroes with no fears of women. The tragic dimension so present in Muslim harems - fear of women and male self-doubt - is missing in the Western harem."', '"Women,Men,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"To me, the Quran is a research book."', '"Me,Research,Book"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"Now that Arab women are pouring into the streets by the million, men discover with dismay that they, not women, were the captives of the harem dream."', '"Women,Men,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"To understand the fanatic rejection of women\'s liberation in the Muslim world, one has to take into account the time factor. Most of us educated women have illiterate mothers. The conservative wave against women in the Muslim world is a defense mechanism against profound changes in both sex roles and the touchy subject of sexual identity."', '"Women,Time,Sex"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"If, by chance, you were to meet me at the Casablanca airport or on a boat sailing from Tangiers, you would think me self-confident, but I am not. Even now, at my age, I am frightened when crossing borders because I am afraid of failing to understand strangers."', '"Age,Chance,Boat"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcec', '"I was amazed to realize that for many Westerners, Scheherezade was considered a lovely but simple-minded entertainer, someone who relates innocuous tales and dresses fabulously. In our part of the world, Scheherezade is perceived as a courageous heroine and is one of our rare female mythological figures."', '"World,Someone,Realize"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'Renewable energy is no longer a niche fuel.', '"Energy,Renewable Energy,Niche"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"We have to use cars much more efficiently. We have to look at alternative technologies of cars such as biofuels or, even more importantly, electric cars."', '"Look,Electric Cars,More"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"When a person from a community goes and buys a car, he or she should have the incentive, financial incentive, to buy a more efficient, more environment-friendly car. This shouldn\'t be only left to the intention of the people. We cannot only rely on the ethics or the moral of the people."', '"Car,Community,Ethics"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"We are considered to be a watchdog, the IEA, and a watchdog fulfils its task only if it barks. So I bark when I think there is a need for barking."', '"Task,Need,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'Renewables are critical in our fight against climate change.', '"Change,Fight,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"When I look at the many energy-using sectors - such as businesses, households, electricity generators, the transportation sector - I see that the business sector is the one which uses the energy efficiency potential the highest, because they know that using energy more efficiently will also reduce their costs."', '"Business,Look,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Humanity\'s future, to say nothing of its prosperity, will depend on how the world tackles two central energy challenges: securing reliable supplies of affordable energy and switching to efficient low-carbon energy."', '"Future,Challenges,World"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Strong policies and innovation can make the difference for energy security, climate change, air quality, and universal access to modern energy services in parallel - in short, building a secure, affordable, sustainable energy system that is available to all."', '"Change,Energy,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'We should not cling to crude down to the last drop - we should leave oil before it leaves us.', '"Down,Leave,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"I think, for OPEC, the main challenge is to have a price level which brings good profits to them, good incentives for the investments, but at the same time, to prevent prices going to very high levels."', '"Time,Good,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Energy is a linchpin of economic prosperity, with energy security, reliability, and affordability key preconditions for sustainable growth."', '"Growth,Energy,Security"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'The energy sector presents exceptional opportunities for governments and investors.', '"Energy,Exceptional,Opportunities"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Governments have always played an important role in energy investment, but this role has been increasing due to both geography and technology."', '"Technology,Energy,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Industry has to find a way. together with the governments, to find new modes, new modalities for transportation."', '"Together,Way,New"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'I have refused to buy a car for the reasons of sustainability.', '"Car,Sustainability,Buy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"I always thought that using more efficient energy sources, pushing the clean energy technologies such as renewable energies are important."', '"Energy,Important,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'I think my biggest fear is having another global war which might have been a result of sharing the primary commodities in the world.', '"War,Fear,World"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'I believe there should be some financial incentives to make the right choice: to make them to buy the right car or not to buy a car but using public transport systems. I believe that these financial incentives are important.', '"Car,Believe,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'The golden era for coal is over.', '"Golden,Over,Coal"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'We should not only look at the short-term economic benefits of fossil fuels but also at the bad news for climate change. We should therefore not greet the fossil fuel age unconditionally.', '"Change,Age,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"I love football, and I love my work."', '"Love,Work,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"Tar sands are attractive, but like biofuels, they will never replace Middle East oil."', '"Will,Never,Attractive"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"The developed, oil-consuming countries can do several things to ease the transition to the new energy order. One would be to boost vehicle efficiency."', '"Energy,New,Efficiency"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', '"India needs three things for its energy sector: investment, investment, and investment."', '"Energy,Investment,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fced', 'Fossil fuel subsidies are a hand brake as we drive along the road to a sustainable energy future.', '"Future,Energy,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', 'I tried my hand at photography and worked with a studio for six months.', '"Photography,Tried,Studio"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I thought of learning cinematography, so I assisted a cinematographer for an ad."', '"Learning,Cinematography,Thought"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I was not getting work, even after auditioning for films. So I started working in a studio as a photographer; I assisted a cinematographer for two ads. I was thinking that I will get into photography or cinematography or assist someone. But then the \'Dangal\' offer came, and I was busy with the auditions."', '"Work,Busy,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I have always been a movie buff and had no interest in any games and sports. I do not even watch cricket, which is one of the favourite games of most of my friends. However, I have become a wrestling fan after \'Dangal.\'"', '"Sports,Cricket,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I found it more challenging to act in a small scene, especially if it has no dialogue and if it is a close-up with only expressions."', '"Small,More,Act"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I had given up on acting because I would go for auditions every day, but nothing would happen."', '"Day,Every Day,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', 'Shah Rukh Khan is the love of my life. I love Aamir Khan also.', '"Life,Love,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"When such acting powerhouses take note of your work and express their appreciation, it is an overwhelming feeling. I could not believe it when Rishi ji tweeted. Then Amitji and Rekha ma\'am sent handwritten letters, which I have read more than fifty times. \'Dangal\' is a very special film for me, and these are my lifetime treasure."', '"Work,Appreciation,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', 'I was very young during \'Chachi 420\' and don\'t remember much now.', '"Remember,Young,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"Kids and adults are treated differently on sets. Being a kid, you can get away with anything, and it looks cute. But as an adult, it\'s a whole new journey."', '"Journey,Cute,New"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('389999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"At one point, I had lost my confidence as an actor, and working again was tough. I started stammering due to lack of confidence. It took time, but things became better."', '"Time,Confidence,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I faced many ups and downs, like any other actor: not getting through auditions or even worse - getting shortlisted and not being selected. Most actors go through the process."', '"Ups And Downs,Process,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"When I was a kid, I didn\'t know how I got into acting."', '"Acting,Know,How"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"When I was growing up, I thought I was getting bored of acting, so I left that. Then after a few years, I started missing it. I left my studies mid-way, and I used to give lots of auditions."', '"Acting,Missing,Bored"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"After so many years of rejection, I felt acting would have to become a hobby rather than a full-time profession."', '"Rejection,Acting,Hobby"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', 'I was about to give up acting when I got the call about being short-listed for \'Dangal.\'', '"Acting,Up,Call"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"When you are doing a long scene, you have dialogue and interaction to narrate the character. But making sense out of facial expression and reacting is difficult. Having said that, I think such challenges are good for learning."', '"Good,Learning,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"Although I started off as a child artist, I left acting in between, as I felt that I was missing the fun of school days. But a little later, I became keen on acting again and started going for auditions."', '"Fun,School,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I started auditioning but at times would feel depressed, as I would get shortlisted but never received the final call. Only when the commercials were released would I come to know that I was not selected."', '"Feel,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcee', '"I auditioned 5-6 times for \'Dangal.\' I was just waiting for the final call, as there were about 15-16 girls who auditioned for the role."', '"Waiting,Final,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"I want people to recognize me for the work I do now as a model, and not something I did three years ago."', '"Work,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"The Broken Bow group is such a great family and seem like a group of tight-knit people. When I looked for a new label, I wanted to feel I could trust everybody. I wanted motivation to be at an all-time high."', '"Family,Trust,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"Basically, I didn\'t know anything about fashion. I was very nerdy; I went to Bryn Mawr and never even noticed models when I was 21."', '"Never,Know,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', 'I want to make a name for myself.', '"Myself,Name,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"I went from not knowing anything to becoming really curious and wanting to know and respecting people in the industry, realizing how hard they work. I will always be thankful for \'Top Model\' for that."', '"Work,Thankful,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"Now that I work as a professional model, I advise people to stay away from any television shows. It\'s a waste of your time; it\'s just entertainment. It\'s not the fashion that we now know."', '"Work,Time,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcef', '"I hear a lot of \'Top Model\' girls say they are dismissed by clients because they recognize them, but it never happened to me."', '"Me,Never,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"If we follow the traditional way of thought, there will always be traditional enemies. Extremist circles from both sides will find causes to give rise to problems."', '"Problems,Way,Enemies"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'Albania is at risk and we are living in difficult times.', '"Difficult,Living,Risk"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"We have gone through everything as a nation - partition, dictatorship, and even anarchy."', '"Dictatorship,Everything,Nation"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"Milosevic will never stop, because he is fighting for personal power in Serbia. The only way to stop him is cutting the functioning of his war machine. He is spending $1.7 million a day on his war machine in Kosovo."', '"War,Power,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'Today in the era of globalization there is no such issue as borders between states of the same nation.', '"Today,Globalization,Nation"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"Kosovo is too close to Europe. It is not only close to Albania, it is close to Greece, Italy, Germany and Switzerland, where there are still many Kosovo refugees. Spontaneous reactions could multiply."', '"Spontaneous,Europe,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"Albania, Macedonia and Greece have managed to create a good partnership in the south of the Continent and are making progress in blocking the spread of the conflict. But any spillover could destroy this European-oriented partnership and create problems for the European Union countries themselves."', '"Good,Progress,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'Most of Albania considers this Government to be legitimate.', '"Government,Most,Legitimate"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'Organising free and fair elections is more important than the result itself.', '"Free,Result,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"That is why we wholeheartedly support the American-led effort to free the people of Iraq. And though we are a small country with a small military, we are proud to stand side by side with our allies in the fight to end the reign of terror in Baghdad."', '"Fight,Effort,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'To rebuild this country will take a long time but we have the mandate and the people support us.', '"Time,Long,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"All sorts of artillery installations, rockets and tank units that are firing on civilians in Kosovo should be neutralized. If that means air strikes, then NATO should carry out air strikes."', '"Air,Carry,NATO"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"We are not only talking about waves of refugees coming to Greece, to Italy, and elsewhere. Destabilizing the Balkans means Lebanonization, and that means destabilizing all of Europe."', '"Waves,Coming,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"Albania does not feel alone. It is part of the Partnership for Peace structures in NATO, and it will do what it can within that."', '"Alone,Peace,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"Thus, neither my government nor myself, personally, are without ideals and responsibilities."', '"Government,Myself,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'Albanians are a nation of freedom fighters who know something about living under oppression.', '"Freedom,Living,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'I am hopeful that no one will forget what happened in Bosnia.', '"I Am,Will,Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', '"If we didn\'t have the Albanian entrepreneurial spirit and financial support from the diaspora, this stupid political class would have destroyed the country by now."', '"Stupid,Political,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'People didn\'t vote left or right in the election. They voted for putting an end to all the primitive political history.', '"History,Political,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf0', 'To see for themselves what the United States has been willing to undertake in the name of freedom. We should all visit Normandy. We should pay homage to those brave Americans who stormed ashore at Omaha Beach and gave their lives for the freedom of others.', '"Freedom,Brave,See"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', '"What offends me the most when I hear criticisms about this so-called Africa bias is how quick we are to focus on the words and propaganda of a few powerful, influential individuals, and to forget about the millions of anonymous people who suffer from their crimes."', '"Focus,Me,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', '"I think my track record speaks for myself... I have been endorsed by the African Union, but I am a prosecutor for 121 states parties and this is what I intend to be until the end of my mandate."', '"Myself,I Am,End"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', '"We say that the ICC is targeting Africans, but all of the victims in our cases in Africa are African victims."', '"Africa,Say,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', 'I am an African and I am very proud of that.', '"I Am,Proud,African"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', 'I am a victim-oriented person. I like to see that the victims know that they have a voice.', '"I Am,Voice,See"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf1', '"I do not think that it is right for me to start giving opinions about the human rights situation of any country, including Gambia, except when those crimes translate into the crimes that I have to investigate."', '"Me,Start,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf2', 'I don\'t believe there is any finer mission on Earth than just to make people laugh.', '"Believe,People,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf2', '"How did I become a star? I don\'t know how it happened. When I look at my old pictures, I can\'t tell how it happened!"', '"Look,Know,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf2', '"I don\'t weigh a pound over one hundred and eighty and, what\'s more, I never did."', '"Never,More,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf2', '"I shall produce nothing that will offend the proprieties, whether applied to children or grownups. My pictures are turned out with clean hands and, therefore, with a clear conscience which, like virtue, is its own reward."', '"Children,Reward,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf2', '"I\'ve never used my weight to get a laugh. That is, used my size as the subject for humor. You never saw me stuck in a door-way or stuck in a chair."', '"Humor,Me,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'Comfort and simplicity are two keys that I follow when it comes to fashion.', '"Simplicity,Comfort,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am diabetic. So diet control is a pre-given for me.', '"Diet,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I read the \'Kapoor & Sons\' script in a half hour, forty five minutes. Not because I skimming through it... I read it like a book. By the end, I was blown away. I picked up the phone and said, \'This script is gold.\'"', '"Gold,End,Phone"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Obviously, I\'m not a man of steel in that people\'s words don\'t affect me. They might hurt me. But I am becoming immune to it as time goes by."', '"Time,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"If I get into something, I get into it for the pure joy of it."', '"Joy,Pure,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Wherever the wind blows me, I\'ll go! My eventual goal is to have enough experience to produce something on my own."', '"Experience,Me,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"My father is pretty much a self-made man, and I am proud of that. He was born in Patiala and crossed the border from India to Pakistan when he was four."', '"Man,I Am,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I have the gift of the gab, can talk and perform, but so can others. I can only attribute it to the fact that somebody up there likes me: it\'s remote-controlled by God."', '"God,Me,Gift"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I was born in Karachi, where my father used to work in the sales department of a pharmaceutical company. The nature of his job required him to travel, so we moved to Athens, Dubai, Saudi Arabia, and Riyadh and then went to Manchester during the Gulf War, moving back to Lahore closer to my father\'s retirement."', '"Nature,Work,War"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I am an immature person, and I am very lazy, too."', '"I Am,Person,Lazy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I was part of a metal and rock band, and I performed in front of 3000 to 4000 people for many years. I was the loudest mouth up there on stage. We would be screaming, head-banging and mass venting. We would all vent our feelings together, which is ideal as compared to participating in political and social forums, and I never felt any restrictions."', '"Together,Political,Feelings"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Whatever appreciation I\'ve got despite the limited work I have done has been great. People have been receptive, and I think it\'s a privilege to have earned this respect."', '"Work,Respect,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Old-world romance underlines my relationships, even with my son and the dog."', '"Son,Dog,Romance"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Everyone has different interests, but instead of constructive learning, people generally tend to lean towards the negative... and I think social media has somehow given fuel to this kind of thinking."', '"Learning,Thinking,Social Media"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"There is so much to learn that I find the entire debate that Pakistani actors shouldn\'t work elsewhere senseless. By working in other countries, we\'re able to move out of our comfort zones, learn more, and bring that back to our own industry."', '"Work,Debate,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I\'m an improvisational actor. I like to do my own thing. But once in a while, I think you should have the self-restraint to let someone else dictate the story."', '"My Own,Own,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I always consider myself as good as my last film. I tend to analyse my work very critically.', '"Work,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Being a part of the Bollywood industry gives you to the kind of exposure that\'s unimaginable. You also tap into this experience of technical expertise that this industry has been carrying along for several years. I didn\'t take part in the industry with an agenda in mind. If it happens, great."', '"Experience,Great,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"As a musician, I have sung, composed, and played instruments, and a lesser-known fact is that I have composed 20-30 ad jingles as well."', '"Well,Fact,Jingles"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"In Bollywood, they\'ve got their systems in place. It\'s a monster machine that\'s churning out, like, 400 films a year, consistently. They\'re able to efficiently process things."', '"Process,Place,Year"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I do give interviews, but I am generally media-shy because I am an introvert by nature."', '"Nature,I Am,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Men are naturally barbarians, and that will remain forever. The passion, the love, and the lust is intensifying with time."', '"Love,Time,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"From the time I\'ve landed in India and wherever I\'ve travelled, I\'ve only experienced politeness and courtesy. There has been no hatred whatsoever. But I strongly feel every country has its formalities and rules that one has to abide by. I believe in respecting that, as it is in the best interests of everyone."', '"Best,Time,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I like to discuss my condition publicly because if I, with this disability, am able to fulfill some of my ambitions, so can other diabetics."', '"Because,Able,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I have always been the black sheep of the family. I am the middle child, with an older and a younger sister."', '"Family,Black,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"The motto of my life is, \'The best advice is no advice at all.\'"', '"Life,Best,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Whenever you move to a new atmosphere, the first few days are difficult. But I always felt that an actor needs to move out of his comfort zone and experience different working environments. And that\'s why I was looking at moving out of my own comfort zones and work with different kinds of people. It helps you grow as an actor."', '"Work,Experience,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I was 17 when I first acted on stage. I was a part of an Urdu adaptation of \'Spartacus\' in the titular role.', '"Stage,First,Role"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I think there comes a time when you start dropping expectations. Because the world doesn\'t owe you anything, and you don\'t owe the world anything in return. Things, feelings, are a very simple transaction. If you get it, be grateful. If you don\'t, be alright with it."', '"Time,Simple,World"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I\'ve adopted a diet that minimises high glycemic index carbs, coupled with lean protein sources and a mix of vegetables."', '"Diet,Vegetables,Protein"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'Almost every story has a romantic angle to it.', '"Romantic,Story,Almost"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I believe you can do a lot even if you have a 15-minute part in a project.', '"Believe,Project,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I don\'t think anyone gets bored of being called good-looking. We are all vain in one way or another.', '"Way,Good-Looking,Bored"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I like playing characters in the real world.', '"World,Real,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Growing up, I loved films like \'A Streetcar Named Desire\' and \'On the Waterfront\' and became a huge fan of Marlon Brando."', '"Desire,Loved,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I stumbled into acting because a friend persuaded me to leave my 9 to 5 job and get into acting.', '"Me,Acting,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I feel - and this goes back to social media and freedom of speech - when you\'re on a public platform, and you put something out there in front of people who don\'t know you, they might just perceive it in a very different way altogether."', '"Freedom,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I have done films only because my roles were good in them. It has got nothing to do with being associated with any particular camp.', '"Good,Nothing,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"\'Khoobsurat\' introduced me to this huge, amazing audience so close to my home. In a lot of ways, it has changed my life, but the game keeps changing."', '"Life,Home,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I\'m married to the only woman I\'ve loved, and I\'m happy."', '"Woman,Happy,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am not finicky at all regarding my appearance.', '"I Am,Appearance,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"If one wants to take a stand on something, one must be very educated about it."', '"Stand,Educated,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"If I\'m going to talk about something, I need to be educated about it, and I need to have seen all the perspectives."', '"Talk,Educated,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I\'ve been penniless. I\'ve had to struggle a bit. But now I enjoy thinking about that because it just makes me feel better about my achievements.', '"Struggle,Thinking,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I may have played romantic roles, but each character has been different, with his own personality."', '"Romantic,Personality,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I have developed my own brand of acting, and fortunately, people like it."', '"People,Acting,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I have been in love with my wife since I was 17. She has always been my strongest support. Even when I didn\'t have this fame, she was there."', '"Love,Wife,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'The time I\'m truly happy is when I\'m playing with my son. We just mentally connect. There\'s nothing more fulfilling than playtime with him.', '"Time,Nothing,Son"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Being trendy is alright, but clubbing all the trends in one look is a complete no."', '"Look,Trends,Trendy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Remember, the fit of your outfit can make or break your look. Ensure the fit is perfect, and you will be just fine."', '"Look,Perfect,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'A lot of men tend to mix a couple of fragrances and smell like a flower garden. Avoid!', '"Men,Flower,Smell"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Fans are half of an artiste... without someone to appreciate him, an artiste is nothing."', '"Fans,Nothing,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"One must be prepared for some surprises in life - some things will work out your way, some won\'t. You just have to keep working and do things to the best of your ability."', '"Life,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I proudly represent Pakistan in India, and I hope that many more actors from there come and work here."', '"Work,Hope,More"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"It\'s a great feeling to be admired... what can I say? It\'s a warm, gooey feeling."', '"Great,Feeling,Warm"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am the kind of person who likes taking one step at a time and raising the bar with each film.', '"Time,Step,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I\'m a quiet person. It\'s only when I am cued to talk that I talk. Otherwise, I\'m reserved and a bit of a recluse."', '"I Am,Person,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I think I\'ve managed to Forrest Gump my way though life.', '"Life,Way,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I self-taught myself music at 19-20.', '"Music,Myself,Self-Taught"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I don\'t think a multi-starrer or a solo film has anything to do with your choice of films. That is a bit of a primitive concept, really. Yes, you might want to keep a healthy balance, but that has more to do with the kind of roles you are playing."', '"Balance,Choice,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'The film\'s content is the king.', '"King,Film,Content"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I choose films preferably based on content, and then I see the kind of team I have to work with."', '"Work,See,Choose"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I was diagnosed with diabetes mellitus Type 1.', '"Diabetes,Type,Diagnosed"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I think I lost too much weight during \'Khubsoorat.\'', '"Lost,Too Much,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I want to play around with my looks. It\'s very boring to appear the same in all your films. Then people are looking not at the character but at the actor.', '"Character,Boring,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"With social media, I think it becomes a little more intrusive. People have more access to you. It\'s obviously very flattering, all the love and affection that you get, and then there\'s also the downside of it: sometimes things don\'t go your way."', '"Love,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I\'d rather speak less because I don\'t consider myself a very intelligent person.', '"Myself,Person,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I\'ve been watching the \'Richard Pryor Show\' for NBC made during the \'70s. I\'m a big fan of his work.', '"Work,Watching,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'My kids are the light of my life.', '"Life,Light,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am the worst strategist ever.', '"I Am,Worst,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am always scared when I start something new. That hasn\'t changed.', '"I Am,New,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"When I started doing television, I had no idea that people were watching it. But then things opened up for television in such a way that it\'s no more \'small\' screen, as it is called."', '"Way,People,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"Television is a big platform for actors, and so many actors have made it to films from there. And for me, too, it has been a great transition from the small screen to the big screen."', '"Great,Me,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"If there is place for music that I do in Bollywood, then I would surely like to sing a song in a Hindi film."', '"Music,Song,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'Bollywood was never on my to-do list. It just happened.', '"Never,Happened,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'My wife is not insecure at all. She is one of the most sensible persons I know.', '"Wife,Know,She"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'My way of deciding whether a film is worth doing is if you can get through it all in the first read.', '"Way,Doing,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I\'ve grown up watching cinema from around the world, and there are films that have scenes that are far steamier than what we are required to do on screen."', '"Cinema,World,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"It\'s always a surprise to me when someone comes up to me and appreciates my work. I have a very limited body of work, so I feel very lucky to have gathered such an audience. I\'m very thankful to them. I\'m extremely grateful to them for showing such love."', '"Love,Work,Thankful"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I wanted to do animation, so for lack of available career counselling, took up Bachelor\'s in Computer Science, but managed to get only C grades."', '"Science,Bachelor,Grades"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"During college, I didn\'t really have an interest in what I was studying. It was during college that I first stumbled into forming an underground band where I was the lead vocalist. I had always had an ear for music, but nothing more than that. And that good ear of mine led me to learn and play a lot of instruments while in college."', '"Good,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I was an angry young man, a rebel without a cause, and I channeled my emotions into my music."', '"Music,Angry,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"\'Khoobsurat\' was an eye-opener in many ways. Cinema is a colossal money-churning business in India, and working in that environment offered me quite an incredible learning experience."', '"Experience,Business,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'You learn a lot about people when you live together.', '"Together,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'The pressure is always there to do my best. I feel happy that I have an audience that looks forward to my next project. I have to make sure that I deliver.', '"Best,Feel,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"There\'s a strong bond I feel with my wife. It\'s not that I haven\'t come across other attractive people in my life, but no one else was willing to put up with me."', '"Life,Wife,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I can\'t even begin to describe what kind of a response \'Humsafar\' got. Personally, I feel my other show, \'Zindagi Gulzar Hai,\' was better, but it didn\'t match the success of \'Humsafar.\'"', '"Success,Better,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'Playing interesting characters makes me feel alive.', '"Me,Feel,Alive"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"As any professional, you go where your work takes you."', '"Work,Professional,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"There is no comparison between the life of a rock star and an actor. If I could now, I would be a rock star within a blink of an eye. So as far as music is concerned, yeah, I might just go back to it, but don\'t want to be unfair to it. It requires its proper time and space."', '"Life,Space,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I\'ve expanded my skill-set through a very limited number of projects and been very lucky with the outcomes most of the time.', '"Time,Through,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"As an individual, I\'ve learnt a lot about life - some things that proved to be helpful and some things I wish I never knew."', '"Life,Never,Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I am genuinely happy that other actors are entering the industry and gaining popularity. There are enough opportunities in the business for everybody.', '"Business,I Am,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"TV needs to be the medium for progress, not degeneration. There needs to be more programming for children. Plays need to become more responsible."', '"Progress,Children,More"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'Television has the power to push for change. We need to push it in that direction.', '"Change,Power,Direction"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I don\'t like it when people remain glued to their phones while talking, so I have no apps on mine."', '"People,Mine,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', 'I wish to direct someday.', '"Wish,I Wish,Someday"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"I observe a lot, and I try to pick out what looks good on me. I like to keep it basic and simple. Never too flashy. Remember, whatever suits you is the best, and it doesn\'t necessarily have to be the trend or the rave of the season."', '"Best,Good,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"My character has to be alive. It can\'t be a mere prop, and it has to have a life of its own. I need to have that space to play around and the scope to interact with the people around me. That freedom would give me a lot of margin to improvise with."', '"Life,Freedom,Space"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf3', '"After I was cast in the acclaimed film \'Khuda Ke Liye,\' I thought it would open up film avenues for me in Pakistan and, maybe, even internationally. When that didn\'t happen, I decided to use TV as a means of polishing my craft."', '"Me,Craft,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', '"I think Col. North is first a U.S. citizen and he has the same rights as you yourself do, sir."', '"Yourself,Sir,First"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', 'We shred every day.', '"Day,Every Day,Shred"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', 'I did not know many of the details relevant to the Iran and contra initiatives.', '"Details,Know,Iran"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', '"And sometimes you have to go above the written law, I believe."', '"Believe,Law,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', '"The press was all over to get a picture of me. It got to the point where they were all over my house, following me to work... Then Tom Brokaw and everybody else was doing stories, \'A star is born.\'"', '"Work,Me,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', '"I felt uneasy, but sometimes, like I said before, I believed in Col. North and there was a very solid and very valid reason that he must have been doing this."', '"Sometimes,Doing,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', 'I was very happy being a secretary. I loved working for the government. I was very happy with my life.', '"Life,Government,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf4', 'I wasn\'t interested in exploiting myself.', '"Myself,Interested,Exploiting"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf5', 'Housework is a breeze. Cooking is a pleasant diversion. Putting up a retaining wall is a lark. But teaching is like climbing a mountain.', '"Cooking,Breeze,Pleasant"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf5', '"A passion for politics stems usually from an insatiable need, either for power, or for friendship and adulation, or a combination of both."', '"Friendship,Politics,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf5', '"Show me a character whose life arouses my curiosity, and my flesh begins crawling with suspense."', '"Life,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"Maybe black and white is the best medium for landscapes, I don\'t know."', '"Best,Black And White,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'I like photographs which leave something to the imagination.', '"Imagination,Leave,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"And in fact I don\'t believe there is such a thing as a definitive picture of something. The land is a living, breathing thing and light changes its character every second of every day. That\'s why I love it so much."', '"Love,Character,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'The viewer must bring their own view to a photograph.', '"View,Own,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"You can\'t expect to take a definitive image in half an hour. It takes days, often years."', '"Image,Half,Days"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"Look at lots of exhibitions and books, and don\'t get hung up on cameras and technical things. Photography is about images."', '"Look,Photography,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"I have always loved reading, so was interested in the literary world, and took many literary portraits."', '"World,Always,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'I hardly teach. It\'s more like a gathering of minds looking at one subject and learning from each other. I enjoy the process.', '"Learning,Process,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"Born Berlin 1931, Germany, father a British diplomat, mother an American artist. Educated at various schools all over the world. 1958 Settled down to live in London. 1966 Became interested in photography through photographing my young children. No formal training."', '"World,Training,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"After Land I wanted to continue exploring the theme but I needed a new challenge so turned to colour. I explored Bradford and produced a series of urban landscapes that I liked, but because Land had made such an impact on the general public my colour work wasn\'t reviewed."', '"Work,New,Landscapes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"But I was, and still am, an avid reader and so when I first started I chose to photograph many of the great writers in this country to try and earn a living."', '"Great,Country,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"It was 1966 by the time I started taking pictures seriously and books, newspapers and magazines of the time were full of great pictures that helped to inspire me."', '"Time,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'I don\'t get wrapped up in technique and the like.', '"Up,Like,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'I had been working in colour for ten years or so and looked at digital and liked the possibilities it gave me.', '"Me,Digital,Colour"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"I have always been a very keen walker, though, and I often took a camera with me on my walks."', '"Me,Always,Camera"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', '"I\'m not faithful to one particular medium, and it\'s what I try to teach to people who work with me."', '"Work,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'I\'ve been working with the land for most of my life; walking it and photographing it. And I love it to bits.', '"Life,Love,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf6', 'What I loathe is the multi-national conglomerates who must take responsibility for the degradation and pollution of so much of our landscape with their factory farming and greed.', '"Responsibility,Greed,Landscape"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', 'This is a coup for commissioner Bud Selig. I\'m surprised it\'s as good as it is.', '"Good,Surprised,Commissioner"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"It\'s tempting, because as one senator said to me, \'We know if we invite baseball down, we\'ll draw a crowd\'."', '"Me,Know,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"Certainly toward the end of the season, you and I could be in a ballpark and they might say the crowd is 30,000, and we could look around and see that there was no more than 10,000."', '"Look,See,End"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', 'The economics of baseball are the big problem. The big clubs make a lot of money and the little clubs don\'t.', '"Money,Economics,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"It was a terrible day for baseball, it was a worse day for Congress."', '"Day,Baseball,Congress"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"I think it would have been a lot better for him to say, I did it and I\'m sorry, McGwire was never one to show a lot of emotion on the field, not a player who sought attention and craved to be thought of as a nice guy."', '"Better,Never,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"I believe that, too, it\'s hard to believe that anybody could not believe that."', '"Believe,Hard,I Believe That"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', 'It\'s not in baseball\'s interest or the players\' interest to be taking this stance. It\'s the people\'s game.', '"Game,People,Baseball"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', 'I can\'t be optimistic. I can be hopeful.', '"I Can,Hopeful,Optimistic"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf7', '"The final ballots represent players, managers, executives and builders who are top-tier candidates and worthy of review for consideration for election to the Hall of Fame."', '"Election,Review,Fame"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', '"Nothing happens, and nothing happens, and then everything happens."', '"Nothing,Everything,Happens"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', '"There\'s no such thing as old age, there is only sorrow."', '"Age,Old Age,Sorrow"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'Beauty is the first present nature gives to women and the first it takes away.', '"Beauty,Nature,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'Only one thing registers on the subconscious mind: repetitive application - practice. What you practice is what you manifest.', '"Mind,Practice,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'Men are irrelevant.', '"Men,Irrelevant"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'I love acting. It is so much more real than life.', '"Life,Love,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'The desire for self-expression afflicts people when they feel there is something of themselves which is not getting through to the outside world.', '"World,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', '"Young women especially have something invested in being nice people, and it\'s only when you have children that you realise you\'re not a nice person at all, but generally a selfish bully."', '"Women,Selfish,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'No one could be more happy than a man who has never known affliction.', '"Man,Never,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', 'People give us credit only for what we ourselves believe.', '"Believe,People,Credit"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', '"The greatest things are accomplished by individual people, not by committees or companies."', '"People,Things,Individual"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf8', '"We shelter children for a time; we live side by side with men; and that is all. We owe them nothing, and are owed nothing. I think we owe our friends more, especially our female friends."', '"Time,Men,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Juan Tripp was a friend. Good name for an airline man, huh? Juan Tripp after another?"', '"Good,Man,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'Only in your imagination can you revise.', '"Imagination,Your,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"I think to have done \'Titanic\' would have been a tortuous experience altogether. I feel good about where my life is, now. I feel free and joyous and happy and more liberated than I have ever been."', '"Life,Experience,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Cary Grant and I were doing a play in New York. He had a crush on me. Whenever we went to a party, he would always sit on the floor beside me. I thought that was kind of beautiful, like that\'s where he wanted to be."', '"Beautiful,Me,New"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Cary Grant was wonderful to work with on stage. He would move downstage, so that as he looked at me the audience had to look at me, too. He knew a lot about the theater and how to move around. He was very secure."', '"Work,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"It was good for us, I suppose. Those kinds of times produce qualities in us that make us better for having had them. My parents were not getting along. My mother was quite intolerant of friendships that were being developed."', '"Good,Parents,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Paul Lucas had a particularly amusing accent, so I chuckled. That was terrible; I shouldn\'t have done that, but he took it too big. He got up and said he couldn\'t work with people who laughed at him!"', '"Work,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"They were very considerate, I must say. Every time I felt I was about to slip out of these fingers and would yell for help, they\'d let me down and re-organize things."', '"Time,Me,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"He was just trying to tease me - I knew that later - but he said he\'d have to leave because it wasn\'t fair to have anyone in the room who was going to make fun of what he had to say. He had a good sense of humor, really."', '"Good,Humor,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"As far as advice, that will be in my next book, my next collection. I certainly never like to instruct anyone, but just say as I feel. That\'s the same as advice, isn\'t it?"', '"Advice,Feel,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Well, the Empire State was about 40\' high in the studio. King Kong was a little model about 2\' high, and the scenery that he worked in was in proportion to his size."', '"King,Scenery,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"I think the studio gave me that series on purpose, because they knew perfectly well that Robert Riskin was ill and that I needed to go to work. They gave me that series to do."', '"Work,Me,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"She wanted us to feel we were above everyone in the town. She really did tell us that we were related to Chief Justice John Marshall, and that may have been true. I never did bother to find out."', '"Justice,True,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"There were shots of Kong pulling at my clothes, but only in horizontal and never from above. Never from above."', '"Never,Clothes,Shots"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'Lillian Gish thought that there should be a cabinet position for the arts and I think she was right. I think she was right.', '"Position,Right,She"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'I don\'t know why Sinclair Lewis fell in love with me. He didn\'t get even the slightest response from me. But his letters were lovely. And the poems he wrote me were lovely. I used some of them in my book.', '"Love,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'There is a lot of strength and intelligence in Hollywood.', '"Strength,Intelligence,Hollywood"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Crawford washed her hands a lot. She washed her arms all the way up past her elbows. She just couldn\'t get enough done in that direction. She was compulsive about being clean, clean, clean!"', '"Past,Direction,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Actually, the camera was never overhead at any time. It was always a side view of me. Subsequently, after the picture was released, I saw some scenes from above and my clothes being pulled-and I think that was added later."', '"Time,View,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'My next book is Scene by Scene: as Seen by Fay Wray. It\'ll be about different incidents. Just my feelings about quite a few people. Attitudes. My thoughts about the universe and simple things like that.', '"Thoughts,Simple,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"That was\' one time when my technique absolutely deserted me, I must admit. There was a wax face that he had created himself to cover his own ugliness. I was in his clutches and I had to hit him in the face."', '"Time,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"I thought I saw him for what he was-or what I thought he was. And he was talented, no doubt about that. But, he thought his talent was based on misery and that if he became happy it would just go. He believed that."', '"Talent,Doubt,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"Sometimes I worked with just a background of a rock or a tree or black velvet, and just had to imagine the whole thing."', '"Black,Tree,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"When the picture was finished, they took me into the sound room and then I screamed more for about five minutes just steady screaming, and then they\'d cut that in and add it."', '"Me,Picture,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"So I was asked to do horror film after horror film, a series of about five, after that, and some of those were a little too gruesome. I wasn\'t too comfortable all the time in those. I didn\'t really care for them."', '"Time,Care,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', 'My children didn\'t when they were little because I thought that they had to be of a certain age. I hoped they liked me well enough not to want to see me in that sort of a spot.', '"Age,Me,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"When it was over my daughter said, \'Oh, I felt so sorry for him - he didn\'t want to hurt you, he liked you.\' That was Victoria. When you visualize him up there on top of the Empire State Building, you do feel sorry for him."', '"Feel,Building,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"For the purposes of the play, it was perfect to be able to use that and the stresses and strains that there were. At the end of the play, the mother realizes the terrible things she had done."', '"Perfect,Done,End"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"I went to Washington to ask for a little residual payment for the people who had written films in the early, early days, people who never got any residuals on tapes or anything at all."', '"People,Never,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"When we were making KONG, I went into the sound room and made an aria of horror sounds. I was in charge of it; there was no one there to listen to me. I was totally in charge of what I wanted to do."', '"Me,Sound,Room"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"The producers who wanted me to do it liked me and trusted me, and more than one scene was only one take, because I\'d plan ahead what I thought would be appropriate for that scene-so one take was enough."', '"Me,Ahead,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"It was so satisfying for me - a great reward, just to see it done well. And it was beautifully directed by my daughter Susan Riskin. Imagine, a play about my mother directed by my daughter?!"', '"Great,Me,Reward"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcf9', '"I would say the secret is to be enthusiastic about everything that comes into your life. To care, to care about people. To be excited about everything that comes close to you. I love to read. And I love to write, mostly."', '"Life,Love,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I always think I would like to have a partner in life, and I would - if I could find the right person, I think."', '"Life,Right Person,Partner"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"When someone is successful, there\'s always a feeling that they were lucky. Luck plays a part, sure, but to be successful, you must have iron discipline. You must have energy and hunger and desire and honesty."', '"Discipline,Honesty,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I am who I am and, you know, I\'ve done the best I can with what I\'ve been given."', '"Best,I Am,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I sort of dropped the ball after \'Bonnie and Clyde.\'', '"Ball,After,Sort"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I regret so much. I\'ve made mistakes. I\'ve hurt people. I\'ve done things I\'m not proud of. But on the other hand, that way lies madness, you know?"', '"Regret,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I want to play real people. Real women. I want to be where the fun is - closer to humanity.', '"Women,Humanity,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Work is a salvation. Work is how you connect with who you are, no matter how painful it might be."', '"Work,Matter,Connect"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I feel like I\'m a beginner in everything in life.', '"Life,Feel,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"The minute you start believing your own success, you\'re on the road to ruin."', '"Success,Start,Road"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Unless you come to terms with your past... it haunts you, and you never leave it."', '"Past,Never,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"God bless McNally, it\'s got some fantastic stuff in it, but it\'s no easy task to make a movie out of."', '"God,Easy,Task"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"If you don\'t eat properly, it affects your energy level. You are an athlete when you\'re onstage. You can\'t get tired."', '"Tired,Energy,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Since Star Wars, that film\'s success led to bigger budgets, more hardware, that the great movies like the ones I did, which were studio movies, are now independent movies. They range from half a million to several million, and a lot of those have very interesting roles."', '"Success,Great,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"You just sort of let them go for a while, but it was time to have something done to my teeth. I\'m glad. It\'s going to be good. Tom Cruise has braces now, too. I\'m right in style."', '"Time,Good,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I\'m still the little southern girl from the wrong side of the tracks who really didn\'t feel like she belonged.', '"Feel,Wrong,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'You are an athlete when you\'re onstage. You can\'t get tired.', '"Tired,Get,Athlete"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Years are not important, my dear."', '"Important,Dear,Years"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'When you\'re younger they always try to get you to do every ninny role that\'s going.', '"Always,Try,Younger"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Well, softness and femininity like yours people don\'t expect of me; so when they find me emotional and capable of real vulnerability, they\'re surprised."', '"Me,People,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"So many people are called but few serve as actors, you know what I mean?"', '"People,Know,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"So Liam and movies are obviously big passions, and I read and write."', '"Movies,Big,Read"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"My mother\'s passion for something more, to write a different destiny for a dirt-poor farmer\'s daughter, was to shape my entire life."', '"Life,Passion,Destiny"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"It\'s true, I did a lot of great movies, and I\'m happy. It was what it was, and now I think all of that has fed into where I am now, and I think it has taught me a lot."', '"Great,Movies,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'It\'s interesting as one grows older to keep in touch with the cutting edge.', '"Edge,Touch,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I\'ve been working on this feature script for Master Class, a play by Terrence McNally that won a lot of Tonys."', '"Master,Play,Class"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I\'m kind of a recluse.', '"Recluse,Kind"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I still have, I hope, a lot of years and there are still a lot of things I want to do."', '"Hope,Things,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I often say the last role I played that really touched me and where I was able to access what I really am was Bonnie, which is kind of sad when you think how early in my career that was."', '"Sad,Me,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I mean, I was always interested in people like Lenny Bruce, people who are breaking the old rules and making new ones."', '"New,People,Rules"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'Do you know what I\'m working on now? My first feature as a director.', '"Know,Do You Know,First"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"All my life, I\'ve been the kind of person who could shatter easily."', '"Life,My Life,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I\'m a loner. I kind of like to be alone and do my work and, you know, be focused on my own things."', '"Alone,Work,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"\'Network\' was formidable in the sense that I was playing a strong, avant-garde woman."', '"Woman,Strong,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"You can\'t be ashamed of the work you\'ve done. You make a decision, and then you have to live with the consequences."', '"Work,Decision,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I didn\'t think my face was beautiful. I guess I found a lot wrong with it.', '"Beautiful,Face,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"When I was discovered, everything happened like dominos. I don\'t know how to talk about it now because it\'s too mindblowing. It\'s so unreal, and yet it\'s real."', '"Real,Know,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'It\'s not age that makes a life. It\'s what you do with it.', '"Life,Age,Makes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Once you reach a certain age, you realize that men aren\'t as important as you once thought they were."', '"Age,Men,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"Acting is different from mental gymnastics. You try to discover as much about the character as you can, but a large area is mysterious."', '"Character,Acting,Mysterious"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"For a long time, I couldn\'t cry on stage. I cried very rarely as a child."', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I get angry when people push people around.', '"Angry,People,Push"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I like the Four Seasons. It\'s a nice hotel.', '"Hotel,Seasons,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', '"I think that somehow I got the notion that I had to be successful, to be the best in the world."', '"Best,World,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfa', 'I was very determined. The straight-A girl. I wanted to succeed. Driven. Let\'s face it: very driven.', '"Face,Girl,Succeed"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'Nothing is impossible on \'Game of Thrones.\'', '"Impossible,Game,Nothing Is Impossible"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'Football is my true love. I played with boys until I was 11 and then for a girls\' club in Middlesbrough until I was 16.', '"Love,True Love,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I\'m from a salt-of-the-earth, working-class, northern background. My dad\'s a steelworker and a firefighter, and my mum is a secretary for the NHS."', '"Dad,Secretary,NHS"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"There were no theatre facilities at the comp that I went to, but I did have amazing teachers who never stopped encouraging me."', '"Amazing,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I\'ve been lucky enough to sort of go over different mediums, different vibes and genres."', '"Vibes,Enough,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"My grandad was a miner. My father, brother, and uncles all work in industry."', '"Work,Father,Brother"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I never expected that I\'d be doing as many jobs as I did. I know everybody says that, but I thought I\'d be sat in my pants waiting for someone to ring me. Then maybe within five years I might get something."', '"Waiting,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'I feel passionately that the opportunities I have had should be available to everyone.', '"Feel,Everyone,Available"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I think, with \'Pride,\' I always knew that was something amazing because of the people who were in it and the story and the way it was written and who was directing. Anyone in that cast knew it was special."', '"Amazing,Pride,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I constantly think I\'ll be found out any second. Some of the crazy stuff that goes through your head. Once you\'ve moved on from the scene, that\'s it: it\'s going in the telly and there\'s nowt you can do about it! It\'s really scary."', '"Crazy,Your,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"Everyone is entitled to their opinion, and you like what you like. But I felt like with \'Pride,\' certainly when it was released in America, there were certain things that went on with the marketing where I though we\'re pandering to whatever the vibe is of that area."', '"Pride,America,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"We are a typical working class northern family, big into our football... no one in the family was into acting. But I remember seeing a panto when I was about six and thinking, \'Yeah... I wouldn\'t mind doing that.\'"', '"Family,Football,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I\'m from the north, so I\'m anti-Thatcher."', 'North', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"Even though I have Twitter, I only use it to say, \'Oh, this is coming out.\' I would never voice anything about me, really."', '"Me,Voice,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"It\'s terrifying, social media. It terrifies me."', '"Me,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'I just like playing people.', '"People,Like,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'I just like doing my job.', '"Doing,Job,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I really loved making \'Love, Nina.\' I was in every scene, which was amazing. Bloody hell, what a job!"', '"Love,Amazing,Hell"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"I like that about London. It comes together when it needs to, and it has magic."', '"Together,Magic,Needs"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'My feet are always on the ground. My family and friends make sure I stay there.', '"Family,Feet,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', 'I worked in a restaurant and in a nightclub cloakroom.', '"Restaurant,Nightclub,Worked"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfb', '"It\'s part of the magic of \'Game of Thrones,\' all the secrets."', '"Game,Secrets,Magic"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfc', 'I was raised thinking that the world would end in 1975 - that Armageddon would come when I was 18 years old.', '"Thinking,World,End"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfc', '"Ever since it was announced that Ryan Murphy intended to produce \'The People v. O.J. Simpson,\' I have been inundated with the question as to \'How do I feel about it?\' All I can say is, for me, it was personally the most heartbreaking tragedy that altered my life forever."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfc', '"Like most people, I shrink from exposing my innermost secrets and my most private and intimate actions."', '"People,Secrets,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfc', 'I\'m not an actress; I\'m not a professional testifier.', '"Professional,Actress"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfc', '"I want nothing to do with O.J. Simpson. I want that name so far behind me, I want it out of my life."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'The only safe ship in a storm is leadership.', '"Leadership,Storm,Ship"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'My satisfaction comes from my commitment to advancing a better world.', '"World,Better,Satisfaction"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"Being a person who has had plastic surgery and goes to the gym five days a week to work my muscles up so they don\'t look atrophied as a 60-year-old, I don\'t disparage people who want to maintain their appearance. But what I don\'t want is a society that tells me I have to."', '"Work,Society,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'A woman who places a high priority on performance and excellence is seen as imperial. A man is seen as demanding and tough.', '"Man,Excellence,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'One of the sad commentaries on the way women are viewed in our society is that we have to fit one category. I have never felt that I had to be in one category.', '"Sad,Women,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"This is not a country that has had a tremendous sympathy for poor people, so I think that the notion that somehow we have slipped into an era in which poor people don\'t matter is not quite the way our history would define it."', '"History,Sympathy,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"I do not make any apologies for my manner or personality. I come from a long line of very strong, black African-American women who neither bend nor bow. I haven\'t had very good modeling in submission."', '"Women,Good,Personality"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'Affirmative action has been generally cast in terms of race. I think women themselves are not as cognizant of the role affirmative action has played in opening the doors for women.', '"Women,Action,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'I have never believed in the impossible.', '"Impossible,Never,Believed"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"I was raised in a very sheltered, narrow environment."', '"Environment,I Was Raised,Narrow"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"My mother taught me a lot of things, but they had big presuppositions built in - like her expectation that I\'d be a missionary nurse in a religious order."', '"Me,Big,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'The influence of one\'s parents is powerful and permanent.', '"Parents,Influence,Permanent"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"\'What can your kids teach you?\' Well, I believe something different about kids. We don\'t own them, they have their own knowledge. From the start you have to make the choice to listen."', '"Knowledge,Believe,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"In 1985, I saw a tape of myself where my eyes were puffy. I looked very tired and bedraggled and not as youthful as I would like to have been."', '"Myself,Eyes,Tired"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'The recognition of rights for women and minorities became a large part of my understanding of what this country is all about.', '"Women,Country,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', 'Many African-American men are incarcerated. And so African-American women do carry an enormous burden. And traditionally have carried a greater burden than perhaps their white counterparts.', '"Women,Men,White"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"We have a very long way to go to really penetrate the power structure. Until that happens, you will not see stability among the workforce, among women - in the workforce among women."', '"Women,Power,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"The deal is that women have entered the workforce, but they have not been relieved of the domestic responsibilities."', '"Women,Deal,Workforce"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcfd', '"My mother was from Mississippi, or is from \'Mississippi;\' my father was from Alabama. He speaks about conditions in Mississippi and Alabama. They were really the poster children for the bad public laws that segregated, according to race, in our country."', '"Father,Children,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"I\'m pretty demanding with myself and my work, and I always put a lot of pressure on myself. I try to do the best job I can every time."', '"Work,Best,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"\'The Omen,\' \'The Exorcist,\' those movies for me are the quintessential horror movies that still scare me as an adult."', '"Movies,Me,Adult"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"As a storyteller, when you\'re writing a movie and when you\'re directing, you want to keep people entertained. That\'s the whole point, right? It has to be entertaining."', '"People,Right,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', 'I have my pride. I\'m a director. I\'m not going to go and recreate some other director\'s vision.', '"Vision,Pride,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', 'Only really good comedies and really good horror movies get a verbal response out of the audience. People will scream. People will laugh.', '"Good,Movies,People"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"Maybe because I\'m a child of the \'80s, but for me, a sequel is a story that follows the previous one, and sometimes if you haven\'t seen the original, then you don\'t understand the second one. Like \'Back to the Future 2.\' If you haven\'t seen the first one, you\'re not going to get anything out of \'Back to the Future 2.\'"', '"Future,Me,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"\'Evil Dead\' was such a big movie in my life. It\'s one of the few that I really remember when I watched it for the first time. I mean, I don\'t remember when I first saw \'The Empire Strikes Back,\' and it\'s one of my favourite movies."', '"Life,Time,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"There are the horror fans that love the \'Evil Dead\' because of the humor, but I\'m sure it\'s not all of them. Not all horror fans love \'Evil Dead\' because of the humor, at least not me."', '"Love,Humor,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"If you think about it, you can have the best CGI, but you can always tell that it is CGI. Your brain can spot that is not real even though you think it looks cool. Your brain knows the truth, so you don\'t jump and you don\'t scream. It was very important for me to expose the audience to real elements."', '"Cool,Best,Truth"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', 'I always say that I am a big fan of films but I am an even bigger fan of the filmmaking craft.', '"I Am,Filmmaking,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"PG-13 horror, I just don\'t watch that."', '"Watch,Horror,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"Every day I spend in Hollywood, I start to realize how many films are made with no heart and no love. They just do it for the paycheck, and I cannot imagine making a film that way."', '"Love,Heart,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"I\'m inspired when I find out about something that I didn\'t know was a remake. An example is, of course, stuff like \'The Fly,\' or \'The Thing,\' or even \'The Blob.\' For our generation, all those things, whether it was \'The Blob\' or \'The Fly\' or something else, we had no idea they were remakes."', '"Fly,Generation,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"In \'Clockwork Orange,\' you\'re there with your eyes, watching all those things, your brain goes off, ahh, exposes you to so many things, and at the end of the day, it\'s just like a roller coaster. Why do you jump in a roller coaster? You want a thrill."', '"Eyes,Brain,End Of The Day"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"It doesn\'t matter the amount of gore, the amount of shocks that you can have in a movie if the movie\'s not entertaining, if the story\'s not entertaining."', '"Matter,Story,Amount"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"A good story will keep you wondering about what\'s happening, what\'s going on, where does this go? Now it\'s going to go that way, now it\'s going to go that way. It has to do that. If it\'s predictable, it\'s just boring."', '"Good,Boring,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"If you think about it, a lot of great horror films have bad sequels just because the market demands you to make the other one right away. Thank God no one in the \'Evil Dead\' family thinks that way."', '"Family,God,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"I\'m a big fan of movies, but I\'m a bigger fan of filmmaking itself. I fell in love with it when I was very young, and I have always loved to learn the craft, every aspect of it."', '"Love,Movies,Filmmaking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"I love just about every aspect of the filmmaking except acting. I would never be able to do that, but the rest I really enjoy."', '"Love,Rest,Filmmaking"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"I watched \'Evil Dead\' when I was 12. I was going through all the horror I could grab. I remember going to the video store and asking for something \'real.\' And the guy gave me the \'Evil Dead\' VHS. When you\'re 12, you\'re not supposed to see that."', '"Me,Dead,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', 'There\'s a reason people use CGI: it\'s cheaper and faster. I hate that.', '"Hate,People,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"A good horror movie - it doesn\'t matter how many comedy horror films there have been before. Doesn\'t matter how much you think it\'s going to be funny. A good horror movie will scare the hell out of you... the moment you sit down and you start being exposed to that story, it\'s going to freeze your blood."', '"Funny,Good,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"As a director, there is nothing more fun than seeing an audience screaming and jumping. You are the ultimate puppet master, controlling the emotions of the audience."', '"Fun,Emotions,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', '"In another life, I would love to be the art guy - a production designer or a maybe even a composer."', '"Life,Love,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:39:00', '2023-05-29 11:39:00'),
	('390345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcff', 'I thought that Hollywood was just for geniuses and that directors come from three generations of directors. I was worried that I was not up to the challenge of making a movie. Then realized that all a director has to do is know what he wants to do.', '"Know,Challenge,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'The European Union is here to stay.', '"Stay,European Union,Here"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Without justice, the most heinous crimes go unpunished; victims are unable to obtain redress, and peace remains an elusive goal, since impunity generates more hatred, leading to acts of revenge and more suffering."', '"Peace,Revenge,Justice"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Indeed, our British friends have decided to leave us - which is very sad for all of us - but life goes on, and the European Union as well goes on."', '"Life,Sad,Life Goes On"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'I think that it is becoming more and more clear that the European Union is an indispensable partner in some fields.', '"Partner,More,European Union"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"In international relations, you don\'t base your work on hope."', '"Work,Hope,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Justice is one of the core elements towards reconciliation and sustainable peace.', '"Peace,Justice,Reconciliation"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Peace between Israel and Palestine is a top priority for the European Union, and it will remain a top priority in our political agenda."', '"Peace,Political,Palestine"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Our policy on the annexation of Crimea, which we consider illegal, will stay."', '"Will,Stay,Policy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"In a changing global landscape, Europe will be more and more an indispensible power."', '"Power,Will,Landscape"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The effect of sanctions on the Russian economy are clear to everybody, first to the Russians and to the Russian leadership, and the surroundings of the Russian leadership, the circle that is close to the Russian political leadership."', '"Leadership,Political,Circle"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'E.U.-U.S. ties are deeper than any change in politics.', '"Change,Politics,Deeper"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"This can sound as something naive. But if we are together in this union, it\'s because we choose to be one in many things. That\'s what makes the European Union experience so challenging and also a model. Why did we do this choice? Because we see that we share a common interest and common values."', '"Experience,Together,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'A stronger E.U. of defence makes NATO stronger.', '"Stronger,Defence,NATO"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Europe, Latin America, and the Caribbean share a cultural heritage based on centuries of common history. And what is more, we share the same values and world view. We believe in a world order that is based on cooperation, on regionalism, on multilateralism."', '"History,View,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"It\'s not diversity that is going to destroy us, but fear of diversity."', '"Fear,Diversity,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Anti-Semitism has not disappeared, and European Jews have too often come under attack."', '"Attack,Come,Anti-Semitism"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We will stand by the Paris climate deal.', '"Will,Stand,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'I\'m convinced the fall of Aleppo will not end the war.', '"War,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'The European Union remains a staunch supporter of the ICC and is committed to full co-operation on the prevention of serious crimes falling under the jurisdiction of the Court.', '"Serious,Falling,European Union"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"I\'d be happy if, during my mandate, the Palestinian state existed."', '"Happy,Be Happy,State"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We do not interfere in U.S. politics... and Europeans expect that America does not interfere in European politics.', '"Politics,America,Interfere"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Each new generation needs to commit again to the foundations of our peaceful coexistence.', '"New,Generation,New Generation"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'The E.U. intends to be one of the biggest humanitarian donors on the Syrian crisis.', '"Crisis,Humanitarian,Syrian"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The European way is also the United Nations\' way. And we believe in the U.N. because we believe in the same principles, in the same values, and our communities are built upon the same fundamental ideals."', '"Believe,Way,Principles"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'It\'s not for me or another European to speak about domestic political choices or decisions in the U.S.', '"Political,Me,Choices"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Jerusalem is not just a beautiful city: the challenge is to show that Jerusalem can be shared in peace and respect.', '"Respect,Peace,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Internal security implies also an external dimension, a defence capacity."', '"Security,Defence,Capacity"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'I will be very involved in Ukraine.', '"Will,Ukraine,Involved"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'The E.U. needs a strategy that marries a shared vision to common action.', '"Vision,Action,Strategy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"There are no regions in the world as reciprocally integrated as Latin America and the Caribbean, and Europe."', '"World,America,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Global issues require common responses: Only together we can create the conditions to defeat Daesh and al Qaeda, block channels for terrorist financing, tackle foreign terrorist fighters."', '"Together,Create,Defeat"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"In the wake of the United Kingdom\'s vote to \'Brexit\' the E.U., we Europeans will indeed have to rethink how our Union works; but we know very well what we need to work for. We know what our principles, interests, and priorities are."', '"Work,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Too often, when Europeans talked of trans-Atlantic ties, we focused on the North Atlantic only."', '"Only,North,Often"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'There is a need for the European Union to use all potential we have on defense cooperation.', '"Need,Potential,European Union"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"As long as a member state is a member state, there are no negotiations bilaterally on any trade agreement with third parties."', '"Long,State,Agreement"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We have to be serious and consistent if we believe the European Union makes sense. I believe it makes sense.', '"Believe,Serious,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Too many times, the international community has not prepared the post-conflict period in time."', '"Time,Community,International"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"We need to have Turkey respect democracy, human rights, and fundamental freedoms."', '"Respect,Democracy,Human Rights"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'It is not only the people of Gaza that can\'t afford having a fourth war - all the world cannot afford this.', '"War,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Our expectation is that the Russian Federation does its part to protect its own citizens in full respect of human rights principles.', '"Respect,Own,Principles"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'There are trends in our societies... that can lead to some political decisions in America and in Europe that can give some ground to the radicalization discourse.', '"Political,America,Trends"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The European Union will never see America, or an American president, as a risk."', '"America,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We Europeans have a long tradition of cultural and economic relationship with Iran.', '"Relationship,Long,Tradition"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Maybe \'America first\' means also that you have to deal with America first.', '"America,First,Deal"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"Our interests are indeed common European interests, and the only way to serve them is by common means. That is why all Europeans, and all E.U. member states, have a collective responsibility to strengthen our Union."', '"Responsibility,Way,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'Moving from Rome to Brussels was hard.', '"Moving,Hard,Rome"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"As it happens in relationships that are open and frank and based on mutual respect, you say things as you think them, and this doesn\'t mean that you don\'t work together in a constructive way."', '"Work,Respect,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The E.U. can deliver on its citizens\' needs and make its partnerships work only if we all act together - E.U. institutions and national governments, at all levels, united."', '"Work,Together,Partnerships"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We need to restart political processes to end wars.', '"Political,End,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'There have always been different opinions on some elements of our sanction policy. It will probably stay that way... What is important is that we keep this unity and decide all together.', '"Together,Unity,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The European Union and its member states continue and will continue, as the nuclear deal is implemented, to have open channels with Iran."', '"Will,Continue,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'We want to engage in ever closer synergy with Latin American and Caribbean partners.', '"American,Synergy,Caribbean"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"There is, and there will be, an increasing demand for a principled global security provider, for a superpower that believes in multilateralism and cooperation."', '"Security,Will,Cooperation"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'No country can become an E.U. member state if it introduces the death penalty.', '"Death,Country,State"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"A transition, by definition, means you start in one place and finish in another."', '"Start,Place,Finish"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"My passion was reading newspapers - and I became curious, in particular, about Islam and the Arab world."', '"Passion,World,Curious"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'An alliance of civilisations can be our most powerful weapon in the fight against terror.', '"Fight,Powerful,Weapon"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"The European Union will continue to fully support multilateral global governance based on international law, human rights, and strong international institutions."', '"Support,Law,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"There is nothing more worrisome to ISIS than cooperation between \'the West\' and the Muslim world, for it defies the narrative of a clash of civilisations the group is trying to revive."', '"World,Nothing,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'A relatively young woman is perceived as younger than a relatively young man.', '"Man,Woman,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'I think Jerusalem can be and should be the capital of two states.', '"Two,Think,Jerusalem"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', '"We need a Palestinian state - that is the ultimate goal, and this is the position of all the European Union."', '"Position,Need,European Union"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'A free trade agreement can be a win-win for E.U. and India.', '"Free,Agreement,Trade"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd00', 'The European vision is the United Nations\' vision.', '"Vision,United Nations,United"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'We need no messiah and no sterile conception of a god menacing us with hell and purgatory.', '"God,Hell,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'The love of liberty and the sense of human dignity are the basic elements of the Anarchist creed.', '"Love,Liberty,Dignity"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'We tried many times before to speed on the social revolution in Spain; attempted to stir up the feelings of the people and to raise the banner of Libertarian Communism.', '"Feelings,People,Communism"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"Authority is something from which we are constantly subtracting, of which there remains always a residue, and which we attempt to make smaller and smaller."', '"Always,Authority,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"The people themselves, and only the people, determine the rhythm of our fight."', '"Fight,People,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"In Spain, we should have enough intelligence, enough sense of individual and collective responsibility to do for ourselves that which would be imposed upon us by a dictatorship."', '"Intelligence,Responsibility,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"Prostitution presents a moral, economic and social problem that cannot be resolved juridically."', '"Moral,Social,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"We have confirmed something we only knew in theory, namely that revolution, in which uncontrolled and uncontrollable forces operate imperiously, is blind and destructive, grandiose and cruel."', '"Blind,Revolution,Cruel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"Men are as we have always known them, neither better nor worse from the hearts of rogues there springs a latent honesty, from the depths of honest men there emerges a brutish appetite - a thirst for extermination, a desire for blood."', '"Men,Honesty,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'I wish to say that we Anarchists have never changed our position. We are Anarchists as of old and still pursue the same ideals.', '"Never,Wish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"Our constancy, same might call it our madness, was necessary to wear down the oppressive forces of the old democracy which, in Spain, was a hundred years behind the times."', '"Democracy,Madness,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'The struggle is so great that the triumph over fascism alone is worth the sacrifice of our lives.', '"Alone,Great,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"There are Anarchists in other parts of the world who are unable to, comprehend the position of the Spanish Anarchists. I do not pretend to censor these Anarchists."', '"World,Position,Pretend"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"If all our comrades of Europe, America and other countries, who do not understand what we are doing to Spanish Anarchism, would come to Spain, we could then see how they would react."', '"America,See,React"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'And we will accept the creation of the Iberian Federation of a socialist republic which will give each region the right to construct its life in accordance with its economic possibilities and political preponderance.', '"Life,Political,Accept"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"There is, therefore, no solution possible other than an economy directed by the workers through their organisations of control-through the workers\' syndicates."', '"Solution,Possible,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', '"In order to fully realise our aspirations, we must create in the masses of the people the sense of sacrifice and responsibility that has been the characteristic of the anarchist movement throughout its historic development in Spain."', '"Sacrifice,Responsibility,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'But we must create in each person a sense of responsibility in order that each one of us can have the right to enjoy all his rights.', '"Responsibility,Person,Create"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd01', 'Never will the Anarchists in Spain be made to suffer as they have been and are in Russia.', '"Will,Never,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'A different language is a different vision of life.', '"Life,Communication,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"If you see with innocent eyes, everything is divine."', '"Eyes,Innocent,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'There is no end. There is no beginning. There is only the passion of life.', '"Life,Passion,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"My relationship with my body has changed. I used to consider it as a servant who should obey, function, give pleasure. In sickness, you realise that you are not the boss. It is the other way around."', '"Relationship,Boss,Sickness"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"Talking about dreams is like talking about movies, since the cinema uses the language of dreams; years can pass in a second, and you can hop from one place to another. It\'s a language made of image. And in the real cinema, every object and every light means something, as in a dream."', '"Dreams,Movies,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'All art is autobiographical. The pearl is the oyster\'s autobiography.', '"Art,Autobiography,Oyster"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'You exist only in what you do.', '"Brainy,Only,Exist"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Experience is what you get while looking for something else.', '"Experience,Looking,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Censorship is advertising paid by the government.', '"Government,Advertising,Censorship"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"In \'Roma,\' I wanted to get across the idea that underneath Rome today is ancient Rome. So close. I am always conscious of that, and it thrills me. Imagine being in a traffic jam at the Coliseum! Rome is the most wonderful movie set in the world... As was the case with many of my film ideas, it was inspired by a dream."', '"Today,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'It\'s easier to be faithful to a restaurant than it is to a woman.', '"Restaurant,Woman,Faithful"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Realism is a bad word. In a sense everything is realistic. I see no line between the imaginary and the real.', '"Bad,Real,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'A created thing is never invented and it is never true: it is always and ever itself.', '"True,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Money is everywhere but so is poetry. What we lack are the poets.', '"Money,Poetry,Everywhere"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'God may not play dice but he enjoys a good round of Trivial Pursuit every now and again.', '"God,Good,Dice"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"Even if I set out to make a film about a fillet of sole, it would be about me."', '"Movies,Me,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Nietzsche claimed that his genius was in his nostrils and I think that is a very excellent place for it to be.', '"Genius,Place,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"I don\'t believe in total freedom for the artist. Left on his own, free to do anything he likes, the artist ends up doing nothing at all. If there\'s one thing that\'s dangerous for an artist, it\'s precisely this question of total freedom, waiting for inspiration and the rest of it."', '"Freedom,Waiting,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"No critic writing about a film could say more than the film itself, although they do their best to make us think the oppposite."', '"Best,More,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"Through the ages, from the beginning of time, I\'m certain man has covered woman\'s face with masks. They are, however, his masks, not hers."', '"Time,Man,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"When I start a picture, I always have a script, but I change it every day. I put in what occurs to me that day out of my imagination. You start on a voyage; you know where you will end up but not what will occur along the way. You want to be surprised."', '"Change,Imagination,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'I am not the kind of director who sits in a chair smoking a cigar talking with a microphone to 10 assistants. I need to move. To touch. To put a painting on a wall. To arrange a set.', '"Smoking,I Am,Painting"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'It is only when I am doing my work that I feel truly alive.', '"Work,I Am,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Fate is written in the face.', '"Face,Fate,Written"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'The artist is the medium between his fantasies and the rest of the world.', '"World,Rest,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"The public has lost the habit of movie-going because the cinema no longer possesses the charm, the hypnotic charisma, the authority it once commanded. The image it once held for us all - that of a dream we dreamt with our eyes open - has disappeared."', '"Eyes,Cinema,Habit"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"If you do what you were born to do, I think you will never grow old."', '"Grow,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"To people of my generation, the picture show was really another dimension - sensual, whimsical. No uniforms or collective rites, but a place where little boys like me could laugh and feel free."', '"Me,Free,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"I make pictures to tell a story, to tell lies, and to amuse."', '"Story,Tell,Pictures"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'Hype is the awkward and desperate attempt to convince journalists that what you\'ve made is worth the misery of having to review it.', '"Review,Worth,Hype"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'My work has always been the thing that justifies my life.', '"Life,Work,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"I think television has betrayed the meaning of democratic speech, adding visual chaos to the confusion of voices. What role does silence have in all this noise?"', '"Silence,Chaos,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"I\'d like very much to make a confident picture. I would like to be as good as nature, which, with a shower, produces flowers and grass to cover the destruction. But we are surrounded by human fragmentation, by pessimism, and it is difficult to talk of other things."', '"Nature,Good,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'A good opening and a good ending make for a good film provide they come close together.', '"Good,Together,Ending"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'I do not need a producer. I need only a good production manager. I need only a man who will give me money.', '"Money,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'I always direct the same film. I cannot distinguish one from the other.', '"Always,Film,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', '"I did not realise that I was so loved. It can\'t just be for the films. I must have done something else, but I can\'t remember what."', '"Remember,Done,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd02', 'All artists are equal when they are themselves.', '"Equal,Themselves,Artists"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"In Spain, the dead are more alive than the dead of any other country in the world."', '"World,Dead,Alive"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', 'The two elements the traveler first captures in the big city are extra human architecture and furious rhythm. Geometry and anguish.', '"Architecture,City,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', 'There is nothing more poetic and terrible than the skyscrapers\' battle with the heavens that cover them.', '"Battle,Nothing,More"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"As I have not worried to be born, I do not worry to die."', '"Die,Worry,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', 'To see you naked is to recall the Earth.', '"Earth,Naked,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"With their souls of patent leather, they come down the road. Hunched and nocturnal, where they breathe they impose, silence of dark rubber, and fear of fine sand."', '"Fear,Silence,Sand"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"Besides black art, there is only automation and mechanization."', '"Art,Black,Automation"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"New York is something awful, something monstrous. I like to walk the streets, lost, but I recognize that New York is the world\'s greatest lie. New York is Senegal with machines."', '"Walk,World,Lie"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', 'Green how I want you green. Green wind. Green branches.', '"Green,Wind,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"The only things that the United States has given to the world are skyscrapers, jazz, and cocktails. That is all. And in Cuba, in our America, they make much better cocktails."', '"World,America,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"I was lucky enough to see with my own eyes the recent stock-market crash, where they lost several million dollars, a rabble of dead money that went sliding off into the sea."', '"Money,Eyes,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd03', '"Not for a moment, beautiful aged Walt Whitman, have I failed to see your beard full of butterflies."', '"Beautiful,Moment,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I\'ve never considered myself as a legend - just a simple man with heart.', '"Myself,Heart,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"A fighter, a real strong fighter, should always look dignified and calm, and I believe that any expression of aggression is an expression of weakness. A strong person will not be nervous and will not express aggression towards his opponent. He will be confident in his abilities and his training; then he will face the fight calm and balanced."', '"Fight,Look,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I\'m very grateful to God for what he gives me. Victories, remarkable victories, but you have to go through the defeats. That is why I praise God for everything."', '"God,Me,Grateful"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I have no special strategy. I can just wait to see what my opponent offers.', '"Wait,See,Strategy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"For every athlete, it is very important to be able to engage in their favorite thing, give all the best in training, performing in competitions, defending the honor of the motherland."', '"Best,Training,Honor"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I never believed I was the best fighter in the world.', '"Best,World,Fighter"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I try and make it possible for beginners to start training MMA and not be scared of it as a sport. I try to actually give them the skill set that is necessary - to feel comfortable, maybe not on a big level. And not just Russia, but worldwide."', '"Skill,Training,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"In my opinion, faith helps in many contexts."', '"Faith,Opinion,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"As human beings, our lives should be in retrospect with God."', '"God,Human,Our Lives"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'No one expected me to become a champion.', '"Me,Champion,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"If people think they\'ve found my biggest weakness, let them try to take advantage of it."', '"People,Weakness,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'It is God who gives us the opportunity to win and to get victories.', '"God,Opportunity,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"Actually, when I fought in PRIDE, we had the best fighters in the world. Back then, the UFC had a very serious and big crisis; they were going through some tough times trying to get top fighters. All the best fighters were in PRIDE."', '"Best,Pride,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I train and prepare for every contest the same so I can compete to the best of my abilities.', '"Best,I Can,Train"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"A true athlete is someone who doesn\'t just stop training when they stop competing. It\'s a way of life, and they keep in shape just to keep up that standard."', '"Life,Training,True"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"Dan Henderson has been a fighter for a long time, and he\'s been a champion in many different organizations."', '"Time,Long,Champion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"UFC is a moneymaking machine. The most important thing for this organization is a brand and its marketing. They have a couple of good fighters, and there are also some very good champions, but they are trying to keep everyone at the same level. The most important thing for them is the promotion, not the fighters."', '"Good,Organization,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I would like to have a rematch against Fabricio Werdum.', '"Against,Like,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"You know when a person goes into the ring to win, or at least not to lose. I mean, when a fighter is ready and goes to fight, than it can be seen by his look. Regardless of whether he gets hit or not, he goes forward, and regardless of whether he wins or loses, he wants to go forward, and it is clear from his burning eyes."', '"Eyes,Fight,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'People are making judgements about Russian people based on me. This is why I never allow myself any aggression towards my opponent.', '"Myself,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I don\'t think about fights that didn\'t happen.', '"Think,Happen,About"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'The UFC didn\'t want me to fight there so what could I do? We were unable to make a deal. They offered unacceptable conditions.', '"Fight,Me,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"Most importantly, you have to stay true to yourself as well as those fans who made you who you are as an athlete."', '"Yourself,True,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"While I\'m an athlete and while I\'m fighting actively, I don\'t intend to pursue a career in politics. What happens after that, we\'ll see. But I don\'t have an intention to do both at the same time."', '"Politics,Time,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"If Dana White can offer a contract that\'s not one-sided, and it\'s not cumbersome to the point where we look at it and realize that we can\'t fight for him, then we\'ll fight in the UFC."', '"Fight,Look,White"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I gain strength out of familiar surroundings.', '"Strength,Surroundings,Gain"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"Cain Velasquez, he has some technical difficulties, but he has ambition, and he\'s fearless. He wants to win so badly, and he\'s in great condition. He\'s a thinking fighter."', '"Great,Thinking,Ambition"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'It\'s essential for a fighter to go separately and just focus on training away from everybody else.', '"Focus,Training,Fighter"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I\'ve always fought as a heavyweight, and I didn\'t see any reason to fight at a lighter weight."', '"Fight,See,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I have fought all over the world, and I am excited to be in \'EA Sports MMA\' because this game is going to show the global appeal of mixed martial arts."', '"Sports,World,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"Training for a fight is never easy, regardless of the opponent."', '"Fight,Training,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I always like and appreciate the support for the fans; I am very grateful to everyone who supports me.', '"Me,I Am,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I always remember that I am a representative of my country, and I always think about the culture I\'m bringing to people."', '"Culture,I Am,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'One needs to live every day according to God\'s commandments. And then any kind of difficulty or unpleasantness will be manageable.', '"God,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I\'ve already fought my share. God gave me a rich, eventful career, and I thank God for everything, but I\'m done fighting."', '"God,Me,Thank God"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', 'I am the face and ambassador of sambo. The organization I\'m working is trying really hard to make sambo a sport on the Olympian level.', '"Face,I Am,Organization"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"When I was competing, I would run daily 20 kilometers, and in addition to that, I\'d put in many hours of fighting and sparring. That\'s why I was always able to keep the speed in the ring. I would train so hard that sometimes it was not only hard to stand up, but it would also be hard to lay down."', '"Daily,Fighting,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"With my victory, I must always remember that I glorify God."', '"God,Victory,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I try to perform honestly during the fight, and I always remember that I\'m a representative of Russia. I try not to bring any aggression. Just honesty."', '"Fight,Honesty,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"I don\'t know how much the other fighters make. But I need to tell you that, for myself, money is not the first consideration."', '"Money,Myself,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"As far as the UFC, if they offer us a fair deal, then we would be open to fighting in the UFC."', '"Fighting,Open,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"In terms of Rogers, I can\'t comment on how other fighters in the UFC would fare with Brett Rogers because that\'s just speculation."', '"Because,Just,Comment"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd04', '"The first thing I saw was that Brett Rogers had his way very quickly - in 20 seconds - with a UFC champion, Andrei Arlovski."', '"Champion,Way,First"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '\'Joy\' to me is a reflection of the life experiences that I\'ve had throughout the first record and kind of having some time and a hiatus. It\'s just like all of those experiences that I had during that period - that growing up period.', '"Life,Time,Reflection"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"I\'m one of those people that I make a song... then I write another song and then I\'m like, \'But this song is so much better than this song,\' and then I kind of ditch that song. It\'s a long process."', '"Long,Process,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"You grow and evolve and as you do that, your art hopefully reflects that change and that growth."', '"Change,Art,Growth"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"The things that drive me are poverty, and pain, and knowing that I don\'t want to end up being alone and I want to do something with my life and I want the name Dobson to remain in everyone\'s heads. Basically, just to rock and be the best performer I can be, and be true, and be real, and give people the real Fefe, nothing fake, all real."', '"Life,Alone,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"It\'s like I\'ve experienced quite a weird and unusual life, you know, being with a mom who\'s a single parent and struggling with money and things like that. It\'s really hard. And it brings a lot of other insecurities in life and a lot of other issues in life, in school and a bunch of other things."', '"Life,Money,Mom"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', 'I believe that we should be able to marry whom ever we choose. As long as both people are willing... I say go for it!', '"Believe,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"When you\'re young you don\'t think, \'This person is going to change your life.\' But when you start recording your own songs, it comes back and reminds you."', '"Life,Change,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', '"I love rock music, I love country music - I love all music, let\'s be honest!"', '"Love,Music,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd05', 'I would love to work with Jack White or Kanye West.', '"Love,Work,White"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd06', '"Suzhou is an ancient city full of old gardens that are very famous in China. It is very beautiful. Plus, I met my boyfriend there!"', '"Famous,Beautiful,City"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd06', '"Wear some mascara, give attention to your eyebrows, and also take care of your lips."', '"Care,Attention,Take Care"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd06', 'I never pass up the chance to shop at vintage stores.', '"Chance,Vintage,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd06', '"I like Chanel mascara because it has the darkest black. For my eyebrows, I brush them through to keep them groomed and in place. And for my lips, I wear lip balm. I use Kiehl\'s Lip Balm #1. It\'s really helpful during fashion week. If I keep up with these three things, I feel like I look very fresh, young, and natural."', '"Black,Look,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd06', '"For clothes and accessories, I love my friend\'s boutique; One by One and UT.LAB for shoes."', '"Love,Shoes,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I often tell my students not to be misled by the name \'artificial intelligence\' - there is nothing artificial about it. AI is made by humans, intended to behave by humans, and, ultimately, to impact humans\' lives and human society."', '"Intelligence,Society,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"The real existential challenge is to live up to your fullest potential, along with living up to your intense sense of responsibility and to be honest to yourself about what you want."', '"Responsibility,Yourself,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"More than 500 million years ago, vision became the primary driving force of evolution\'s \'big bang\', the Cambrian Explosion, which resulted in explosive speciation of the animal kingdom. 500 million years later, AI technology is at the verge of changing the landscape of how humans live, work, communicate,and shape our environment."', '"Work,Technology,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"There\'s a great phrase, written in the \'70s: \'The definition of today\'s AI is a machine that can make a perfect chess move while the room is on fire.\' It really speaks to the limitations of AI. In the next wave of AI research, if we want to make more helpful and useful machines, we\'ve got to bring back the contextual understanding."', '"Great,Today,Fire"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Technology could benefit or hurt people, so the usage of tech is the responsibility of humanity as a whole, not just the discoverer. I am a person before I\'m an AI technologist."', '"Technology,Humanity,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"If our era is the next Industrial Revolution, as many claim, AI is surely one of its driving forces."', '"AI,Revolution,Industrial Revolution"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'The tools and technologies we\'ve developed are really the first few drops of water in the vast ocean of what AI can do.', '"Water,Drops,AI"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'I believe in human-centered AI to benefit people in positive and benevolent ways.', '"Positive,Believe,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"As a technologist, I see how AI and the fourth industrial revolution will impact every aspect of people\'s lives."', '"People,Impact,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I imagine a world in which AI is going to make us work more productively, live longer, and have cleaner energy."', '"Work,World,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I believe in the future of AI changing the world. The question is, who is changing AI? It is really important to bring diverse groups of students and future leaders into the development of AI."', '"Future,Believe,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'Weaponized AI is probably one of the most sensitized topics of AI - if not the most.', '"AI,Most,Topics"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"As one of the leaders in the world for AI, I feel tremendous excitement and responsibility to create the most awesome and benevolent technology for society and to educate the most awesome and benevolent technologists - that\'s my calling."', '"Technology,Society,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"We all have a responsibility to make sure everyone - including companies, governments, and researchers - develop AI with diversity in mind."', '"Mind,Responsibility,Diversity"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"No one tells a child how to see, especially in the early years. They learn this through real-world experiences and examples."', '"See,Through,Child"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"When I was a graduate student in computer science in the early 2000s, computers were barely able to detect sharp edges in photographs, let alone recognize something as loosely defined as a human face."', '"Alone,Science,Computers"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"AI is everywhere. It\'s not that big, scary thing in the future. AI is here with us."', '"Future,AI,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'Smart CEOs should be thinking about AI and its impact on their respective business.', '"Business,Thinking,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'AI-assisted driving is a perfect platform for advancing fundamental human-centric artificial intelligence research while also producing practical applications.', '"Intelligence,Perfect,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"We will not only use the machines for their intelligence, we will also collaborate with them in ways that we cannot even imagine."', '"Intelligence,Will,Imagine"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I believe AI and its benefits have no borders. Whether a breakthrough occurs in Silicon Valley, Beijing, or anywhere else, it has the potential to make everyone\'s life better for the entire world."', '"Life,Believe,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'There is great potential to use computer vision technology in a constructive and benevolent way.', '"Technology,Great,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"For me it\'s very important to think about AI\'s impact in the world, and one of the most important missions is to democratize this technology."', '"Technology,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"The only path to build intelligent machines is to enable it with powerful visual intelligence, just like what animals did in evolution."', '"Intelligence,Path,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'I consider the pixel data in images and video to be the dark matter of the Internet.', '"Internet,Dark,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'I really believe there are no borders for science.', '"Science,Believe,Borders"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"As nature discovered early on, vision is one of the most powerful secret weapons of an intelligent animal to navigate, survive, interact, and change the complex world it lives in."', '"Nature,Change,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I didn\'t make a lot of friends in high school. It\'s a cruel time, and I was very geeky."', '"Time,School,Cruel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'Understanding vision and building visual systems is really understanding intelligence.', '"Intelligence,Vision,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Besides publishing its own work, the Google AI China Center will also support the AI research community by funding and sponsoring AI conferences and workshops and working closely with the vibrant Chinese AI research community."', '"Work,Community,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'We need to inject humanism into our AI education and research by injecting all walks of life into the process.', '"Life,Education,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'One thing ImageNet changed in the field of AI is suddenly people realized the thankless work of making a dataset was at the core of AI research.', '"Work,Research,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"This is the world where our children will live, and technology should reflect that diverse world. With technology and a little love, we can make it a better place for them."', '"Love,Technology,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"AI will impact every industry on Earth, including manufacturing, agriculture, health care, and more."', '"Health,Care,Agriculture"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'The day healthcare can fully embrace AI is the day we have a revolution in terms of cutting costs and improving care.', '"Day,Care,AI"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'Even a cat has things it can do that AI cannot.', '"AI,Things,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"If someone has a fantastic biology background, he or she can contribute in AI and health care. AI has many aspects."', '"Health,Care,Biology"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Governments can make a greater effort to encourage computer science education, especially among young girls, racial minorities, and other groups whose perspectives have been underrepresented in AI."', '"Education,Science,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I\'m a go-getter. It\'s in my DNA. If I spend a lot of time lamenting on the difficulties, then it could be distracting."', '"Time,Difficulties,DNA"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'Autonomous driving provides a scenario where AI can deliver smart tools for assistance in decision-making and planning to human drivers.', '"Smart,Planning,AI"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'We talk a lot about building benevolent technology. Our technology reflects our values.', '"Technology,Building,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Just like the brain consists of billions of highly connected neurons, a basic operating unit in a neural network is a neuron-like node. It takes input from other nodes and sends output to others."', '"Brain,Connected,Others"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'It is deeply against my principles to work on any project that I think is to weaponize AI.', '"Work,AI,Principles"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"If you were a computer and read all the AI articles and extracted out the names that are quoted, I guarantee you that women rarely show up. For every woman who has been quoted about AI technology, there are a hundred more times men were quoted."', '"Women,Men,Technology"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Yes, we have prototyped cars that can drive by themselves, but without smart vision, they cannot really tell the difference between a crumpled paper bag on the road, which can be run over, and a rock that size, which should be avoided."', '"Vision,Drive,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"I love Silicon Valley, but there is a dominant voice of, \'Tech is cool. Tech is geeky. Tech is a guy with a hoodie.\'"', '"Love,Cool,Valley"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"From the day an idea is conceptualized to the day the technology is built, carried out, and regulated, it\'s important to have that human awareness."', '"Technology,Awareness,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'I don\'t know what would happen if the media starts picking up a theme that Google is secretly building AI weapons or AI technologies to enable weapons for the defense industry.', '"Media,Building,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"Making AI more sensitive to the full scope of human thought is no simple task. The solutions are likely to require insights derived from fields beyond computer science, which means programmers will have to learn to collaborate more often with experts in other domains."', '"Science,Simple,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"What makes humans unique is that evolution gave us the most incredible and sophisticated vision system, motor system, and language system, and they all work together."', '"Work,Vision,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', 'The cloud is this gigantic computing vehicle that delivers computing services to every single industry.', '"Vehicle,Cloud,Industry"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"The paradigm shift of the ImageNet thinking is that while a lot of people are paying attention to models, let\'s pay attention to data. Data will redefine how we think about models."', '"Thinking,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"When eyes were first developed in animals, suddenly animal life becomes proactive."', '"Life,Eyes,Animal"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"As for me, I\'m an optimist."', '"Me,Optimist"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd07', '"AI cloud is just very, very nascent."', '"AI,Cloud,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"The truth is that killing innocent people is always wrong - and no argument or excuse, no matter how deeply believed, can ever make it right. No religion on earth condones the killing of innocent people; no faith tradition tolerates the random killing of our brothers and sisters on this earth."', '"Faith,Truth,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"\'Jihad\' can mean holy war to extremists, but it means struggle to the average Muslim."', '"War,Struggle,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'I condemn everyone and anyone who commits acts of terrorism. And Hamas has committed acts of terrorism.', '"Terrorism,Everyone,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Religion is defined by the relationship between God and man. And Islam is the submission and the acknowledgment of the human being to the creator.', '"God,Relationship,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I worked as a teacher in the public school system in New York City for several years, and I was a victim of the layoffs, you know, in the mid-\'70s. And then I worked as a sales engineer for a company in New Jersey that was selling industrial filtration equipment."', '"Teacher,City,New"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"The ultimate vision is to instate in the Muslim world the notion of multiculturalism, which is part of our heritage and history, part of the fundamental, mainstream ideals of Islam."', '"History,Vision,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"God says in the Quran that there is only one true religion, God\'s religion. It\'s the same theme that God revealed to all of the prophets, even before Muhammad."', '"God,Religion,True"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"The fundamental idea which defines a human being as a Muslim is the declaration of faith: that there is a creator, whom we call God - or Allah, in Arabic - and that the creator is one and single. And we declare this faith by the declaration of faith, where we... bear witness that there is no God but God."', '"Faith,God,Allah"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"The Islamic method of waging war is not to kill innocent civilians, but it was Christians in World War II who bombed innocent civilians in Dresden and dropped the nuclear bomb on Hiroshima, neither of which were military targets."', '"War,World,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"In the Muslim world, there are many people who have been vocal and we have been very vocal against extremists. But how to win this battle is an ongoing battle. And we must continue to wage the battle for peace."', '"Peace,Battle,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"Koran says whoever believes in God in the last day shall be saved. It is a religion whose very name, Islam, comes from the word Shalom, which means peace. It\'s about establishing peace. We greet each other with peace be upon you, which the Jews do in greeting each other."', '"God,Peace,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'We are not going to toy with our religion or any other. Nor are we going to barter. We are here to extend our hands to build peace and harmony.', '"Peace,Religion,Harmony"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'My life has been devoted to peacemaking.', '"Life,My Life,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"We\'ve got to be fair. You can\'t say a place that has strip joints is sacred ground. We\'ve got to be just. We\'ve got to speak the truth. We\'ve got to have justice for everybody. We\'re a country of justice for all, not justice for non-Muslims only or some groups and not for others."', '"Truth,Justice,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I have never made a threat. I\'ve never made a threat, never expressed a threat, never - I\'ve never - I would never threaten violence ever, because I am a man of peace, dedicated to peace."', '"Peace,Man,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'We are Americans. We - we - we are - we are doctors. We are investment bankers. We are taxi drivers. We are store keepers. We are lawyers. We are - we are part of the fabric of America. And the way that America today treats its Muslims is being watched by over a billion Muslims worldwide.', '"Today,America,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'The battleground has been moderates of all faith traditions in all the countries of the world against the radicals of all faith traditions in all parts of the world.', '"Faith,World,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"In spite of the polls, the fact is that American Muslims are very happy and they thrive in this country."', '"Country,Thrive,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"One of the misperceptions that exists in the Muslim world, which needs to be fixed, is the perception that Muslims in America are - are - are living in - in very, very, very bad circumstances. They cannot practice religion freely. It is not the truth at all. The fact is, we are practicing. We fast, we pray, we do our prayers."', '"Truth,Religion,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"The thing about the Islamic situation is we don\'t have a church. We don\'t have an ordained priesthood, which makes it a little complicated. But we do have a tradition of scholarship, and rules of scholarship. It\'s very much like any field of knowledge."', '"Knowledge,Situation,Rules"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"You take the best of our tradition as a start, and I\'ll take the best of Christianity ... From there we can build."', '"Best,Start,Tradition"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Bigotry toward any faith community cannot have any place in civilized society anywhere in the world.', '"Faith,Society,Community"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"Islamic law is clearly against terrorism, against any kind of deliberate killing of civilians or similar \'collateral damage.\'"', '"Law,Terrorism,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Fanaticism and terrorism have no place in Islam.', '"Place,Terrorism,Islam"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'There are always people who will - who will do peculiar things and think that they are doing things in the name of their religion.', '"Religion,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"There are individuals who are working very hard to promote fear and antagonism towards Islam and Muslims in this country. It\'s fueled, in part, by the first African-American president that we have. Obama\'s father was a Muslim and people have used this to arouse hostility against him."', '"Fear,Father,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"A kind of racism still exists in the United States, and Islamophobia is a more convenient way to express that sentiment. There has also been an attempt to paint Muslims as enemies of the United States."', '"Way,Enemies,More"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I\'ve spoken with friends who are rabbis and priests and we\'ve agreed that most people have an emotional attachment to their faith, a desire to fulfill their spiritual longings, but they are not experts in understanding the history of their religion."', '"Faith,History,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I was completely surrounded by religion from a young time. I was taught by my father. I engaged in discussions with him and many of these scholars who visited and came around the dining table, the lunch table, and attended many lectures with my dad. And so I learned the apprentice way."', '"Time,Religion,Dad"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I read, read enormously on all different fields of Islamic thought, from philosophy to Islamic literature, poetry, exegeses, knowledge of the Hadith, the teachings of the prophet. That\'s how I trained myself. And then I was appointed imam by a Sufi master from Istanbul, Turkey."', '"Knowledge,Poetry,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"There are moderates in Israel. There are moderates in Iran, there are moderates in the Republican Party, moderates in the Democratic Party. What we need to do is we need link all of these moderates together and to figure out a way by which this particular coalition can speak to important issues to marginalize the voice of the extremists."', '"Together,Way,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Our enemy is not Islam. Islam is not the enemy of America; Americans are not the enemy of Islam. Our real enemy is extremism and radicalism.', '"America,Enemy,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Any organization or any individual that targets civilians and kills them for political agenda is a terrorist organization.', '"Political,Organization,Individual"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'The American principles of democracy expresses the deepest values of the Sharia both structurally and in the government... Sharia requires us Muslims anywhere to abide by the law of the land.', '"Government,Democracy,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I\'m not an agent from any government, even if some of you may not believe it. I\'m not. I\'m a peacemaker."', '"Government,Believe,May"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'I am a supporter of the state of Israel.', '"I Am,State,Israel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I am an American citizen born in Kuwait of Egyptian parents. I grew up in Great Britain, Malaysia, and Egypt and have lived in the United States since 1965, when I was seventeen."', '"Great,I Am,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"When I arrived in America, I experienced serious culture shock. For someone with a religious upbringing, the 1960s were an extremely difficult time. Even though religion was a big part of the civil rights and peace movements, in my college religion was treated as irrelevant, hopelessly stodgy, and behind the times."', '"Time,Peace,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"In Malaysia, where Western culture was extremely influential, I\'d grown up listening to Elvis and the Beatles and watching American movies. People wanted to be like Americans. In contrast, when I got here, I saw prosperous middle-class American college students wanting to somehow join the Third World."', '"Movies,Culture,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"Staying chaste until marriage, a commandment of my faith, was one of the most difficult challenges of my young life. I had a powerful sense that if I did not get a grip on my identity, my ethics, and my religion, I would go off the rails."', '"Life,Faith,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"If Muslims curse the Christians, then the Christians will curse the Muslims. And people will curse Allah, and Allah will hold us responsible for that."', '"Allah,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"In the 20th century, the Muslim world created a vision of religious nationalism. Turkey, for example, had to be ethnically Turkish. Kurds, Armenians, other minorities didn\'t have a place in such a vision of a nation-state."', '"Vision,World,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"What\'s brilliant about the United States system of government is separation of power. Not only the executive, legislative, judicial branches, but also the independence of the military from civilians, an independent media and press, an independent central bank."', '"Power,Independence,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'The world wants to like America.', '"World,America,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Americans must outgrow the unbecoming arrogance that leads us to assert that America somehow owns a monopoly on goodness and truth - a belief that leads some to view the world as but a stage on which to play out the great historical drama: the United States of America versus the Powers of Evil.', '"Truth,Great,View"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"Sufis teach that we first must battle and destroy the evil within ourselves by shining upon it the good within, and then we learn to battle the evil in others by helping their higher selves gain control of their lower selves."', '"Good,Battle,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"What\'s right with America and what\'s right with Islam have a lot in common. At their highest levels, both worldviews reflect an enlightened recognition that all of humankind shares a common Creator - that we are, indeed, brothers and sisters."', '"America,Recognition,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"It is part of my responsibility as a bridge builder to speak the truth about what\'s great about America, what we\'ve done right, and what our less glorious moments. And many people feel that the Iraq adventure, for example, has been one of our less glorious moments."', '"Truth,Great,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', '"I as a Muslim want you, as a Christian, to really be a perfect Christian. I want my Jewish friends to be perfect Jews, to live according to the highest principles of what it means to be a Jew, to be a Christian, to be a Muslim."', '"Perfect,Live,Principles"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'We tend to forget in the West that the United States has more Muslim blood on its hands than Al Qaeda has on its hands of innocent non-Muslims.', '"Innocent,Hands,Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd08', 'Yusuf Qaradawi is probably the most well-known legal authority in the whole Muslim world today.', '"Legal,Today,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I\'m a Canadian. Outside Canada I carry the flag. Canadian nationalism isn\'t as insidious as American nationalism, though. It\'s good natured. It\'s all about maple syrup, not war."', '"War,Good,Canada"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"So, I\'m on \'Sesame Street,\' walking around with all these monsters, Elmo and his buddies, a whole bunch of chickens, a whole bunch of penguins and a number four dancing about. It was just pure joy, simple, ridiculous fun, stupid joy. There\'s no irony. \'Sesame Street\' is just a crazy great place to be."', '"Great,Stupid,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'There\'s nothing better than not knowing what\'s going to happen until you put the pieces together.', '"Together,Better,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"On the videos for \'1234\' and \'My Moon My Man\' I wanted to make the songs visible. And, really, what way can you make sound visible other than good old naive dancing? I was working with a choreographer, but I\'m not a dancer. Any notion of elegance is impossible with me."', '"Good,Moon,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"There\'s a crazy amount of goodwill, and I don\'t know where it came from, and I don\'t understand, but the more I pay attention to it, the more it\'s going to sting when it flips, so I think I\'m almost subconsciously cultivating this naivety to it all."', '"Crazy,Know,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I get really scared about how the Internet is shifting and changing everyone\'s minds, and the way we see ourselves and interact online. Everything is so diluted now."', '"Internet,Way,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Well, there\'s just some universal truths in a way that I\'ve just observed to be true. You read Voltaire. You read modern literature. Anywhere you go, there\'s these observations about romantic love and what it does people, and these rotten feelings that rarely are people meaning to do that to each other."', '"Love,Romantic,True"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"And of course, pop music is all about memorability and simplicity and positive messages and a little dash of joy."', '"Positive,Music,Joy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'There\'s real potency in metal. Metal fans love metal as if it\'s a nation they would fight for. It\'s not diluted by pop culture.', '"Love,Fight,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Music is pretty intimate stuff and I can only work with very few people: Gonzalez being one, Mocky being another and, on a completely different level, Broken Social Scene. With Broken Social Scene it\'s not one-on-one, it\'s a one-on-12. It\'s very healthy, very comfortable, like a big pot luck supper among old friends."', '"Work,Music,Old Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I was a bar-back, which is the person who cleans the bathrooms at the end of the night in the bar, and a cook. I had kind of given up. I was into backing other people up. Music was something I just did on the side and I don\'t think I had the energy to pimp myself out, like call people up and ask them to book me to play."', '"Music,Myself,Night"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"After \'Sesame Street,\' it\'s a hyper-familiar world to me and I have this childlike ability to ignore the fact that I\'m talking to scraps of cloth. Every country I go to, I see posters promoting the film in different languages. \'Los Muppets\' - I love that!"', '"Love,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I once looked over the shoulder of a friend on Facebook and it looked like hieroglyphs to me. There\'s merit online, of course, but social media gets super freaky. Imagine if three generations from now, people online have forgotten what date or day of the week it is."', '"Me,Social Media,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"When I did \'1,2,3,4\' on \'Sesame Street\' they\'d rewritten the song and made it about counting. At first, I balked. I was like, \'Counting to four? That\'s where we\'re going with this?\' Then they sent me appearances by other people like James Blunt doing \'You\'re Beautiful\' as \'My Triangle.\'"', '"Beautiful,Me,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"When I was in Beck\'s world, I felt like the little sister. I\'m in the big brother\'s room with all his friends. You just hang out and keep your mouth shut so they don\'t realize you\'re there and kick you out. I like being in situations where I can be an underdog, where I can be in the corner and observe and soak it in."', '"World,Underdog,Mouth"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"\'Gatekeeper\' was sort of my first attempt to put a little bit of a frame and boundaries around songwriting, and try to figure out a way to approach it that had a sort of end result in mind. I haven\'t written many like that."', '"Mind,Result,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I guess I found it useful to realise that everything is true at once, you know? You can pull back and say, \'Everything will be fine,\' but you can also be in a situation and say, \'Not everything is going to be fine.\'"', '"True,Situation,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"There have been times I\'ve planted stuff in songs where four years later I\'ll be singing it from a subconscious, kind of chameleon little lizard mind... and at a certain moment, all of a sudden, I\'ll hear a line from a different vantage point and it\'ll change its meaning. It\'s something I wrote but it changed because I did."', '"Change,Moment,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"When you say something or sing something enough times, it becomes a self-fulfilling prophecy. It\'s almost like casting spells. I don\'t mean necessarily in the flighty, \'I\'m going to go buy a cloak with a hood now\' way."', '"Way,Hood,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'I didn\'t really get London until I read Dickens. Then I was charmed to death by it.', '"Death,Get,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '\'Metals\' has partly been about me regaining my self respect and I feel like I\'m growing the muscles I want to grow again.', '"Respect,Me,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"The idea of having one ensemble do everything is what was on \'Sea Lion\' and that\'s what I tried to make happen for \'Metals,\' which is having five people in the room and all of us contributing equally to every arrangement and every song."', '"Lion,Song,Sea"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"You\'re an enormous sponge and everything goes in there and you squeeze it out in songs, I guess. And if you\'re a painter, you squeeze them out on to a canvas."', '"Canvas,Everything,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I\'d been touring for so long, seven years. For a year and a half I\'d just been curious about what it was like not to tour. It\'s like if you were to lift a 100-pound barbell with your right arm for seven years, eventually you\'d get really curious about what your left arm was capable of."', '"Long,Curious,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Surreal can be exciting and good, and it can be like living inside an alien landscape, and it can be completely interesting, or you can be alienated from your own life - inside your own life, it doesn\'t feel familiar any more."', '"Life,Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"If you keep bashing your head against the same wall, at some point you\'re going to fall over and be still for awhile."', '"Fall,Your,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Any kind of anthemic song, for the most part, they\'re on the positive side of things. It\'s not hard to identify when a melody is just one degree too complicated or one degree too simple and where that line of pop memorability lies."', '"Positive,Simple,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I\'ve not really spent much time in proper studios. The room itself where you\'re recording, and how you live while you\'re there is what appeals to me."', '"Time,Me,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Something that I think I figured out slowly was if you\'re playing a show and there\'s a chatter or there is, you know, a lot of noise - people talking or something - I was never the one whose instinct was to try to be louder than them."', '"People,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"When I first played \'1234\' it was on stage in San Francisco at some kind of, like, sticky-floored club. And it felt like a punk song. I mean it\'s ridiculous to say that now, but it had that kind of, like, piercing straight melody. And then this fist-pumping ending, you know that pa-dap-pada."', '"Song,Ending,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I made the first Feist album in \'98. So at that point, it was my nickname. It was as far as with my circle of friends, and just felt more accurate than two names."', '"Circle,More,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"For me, music is in the choice of what not to play as much as in what you\'ve chosen to play."', '"Music,Me,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'You never know what\'s going to play into what\'s worthy of getting encapsulated into a song.', '"Song,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'I live and die by puns.', '"Die,Live,Puns"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'I need therapy after writing. It\'s like leaking blood from a stone. It\'s brutally difficult but worth it.', '"Difficult,Stone,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Opinions are like snowflakes, you know what I\'m saying?"', '"Know,Opinions,Saying"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', 'Commercialism isn\'t challenging creatively; it\'s only challenging in a stamina way.', '"Way,Only,Stamina"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"I remember doing my mosaics or being in my little hiding place behind the couch snooping. I\'d get bored sometimes, of course, but I think that\'s good for a kid, because it forces you to be creative."', '"Good,Remember,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"When I wrote \'Mushaboom\', I was living in the second verse, but I suddenly found myself in the first."', '"Myself,Living,First"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"As I get older, the present and the past shift and become the past and the future... A lot of it is a new awareness of time and life and the wheel of fortune crushing you and lifting you and crushing you and lifting you."', '"Life,Future,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Since I was 19, I\'ve always gone where there was a reason to be. Maybe I\'ll be lucky and there\'ll be a reason to go somewhere tropical for a while."', '"Always,Go,Somewhere"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"There\'s no mystery any more. So my instinct is to show very little, because there\'s much too much information about everyone, everywhere right now. Reality TV is an example of that."', '"Reality,Information,Mystery"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"Musically, I didn\'t relate to Berlin. There seemed to be a lot of machine music made there - I don\'t think I saw a stringed instrument in two years."', '"Music,Two,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd09', '"The group-effort sound in recording of \'Sea Lion\' is like, you really hear all the people in the room and hear them interlocking. There\'s a real freight-train energy of all these people at the same time playing."', '"Time,Lion,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'The human spirit is stronger than any government or institution.', '"Government,Spirit,Stronger"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"The African mind has a lot to contribute, not only to world understanding of the arts, but to an understanding of spiritualism. That is the contribution Africa will make to the world of the future - an injection of sanity into the environment of the universe itself."', '"Future,World,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'A police uniform is just a piece of clothing sewn by the same tailors who sew your clothes.', '"Police,Uniform,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"When you start to think of revenge, you start to think of hate. I don\'t believe in hating people. It\'s a retrogressive thing."', '"Revenge,Hate,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Spiritually speaking, every human being has a destiny and a duty to perform."', '"Destiny,Duty,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'Music must awaken people to do their duty as citizens and act.', '"Music,People,Duty"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Without Tony Allen, there would have been no Afrobeat."', '"Without,Would,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"I\'ve suffered quite a lot, to the point where I\'ve experienced death. Years before I wasn\'t fit to die, but I understand life better now. Death is nice, death is beauty."', '"Life,Beauty,Death"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'I realized that you cannot think European and want to write or create something African. You have to think African in everything.', '"Create,Everything,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"The rhythm, the sounds, the tonality, the chord sequences, the individual effect of each instrument and each section of the band - I\'m talking about a whole continent in my music."', '"Music,Band,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Art itself is knowledge of the spiritual world. Art is information from higher forces, by those who are talented. I\'m not jiving."', '"Knowledge,Art,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"In America we talk about South Africa, but I tell people that apartheid is nothing compared to what is happening in my country where black oppresses black."', '"Black,America,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'Being African didn\'t mean anything to me until later in my life.', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"I believe in pan-Africanism. This means that in many things - the judiciary, sports, economics and trade - we want Africanism to be involved, which is basically more freedom for the people."', '"Freedom,Sports,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"If a female wants to do a man\'s job, no one will stop her from doing it, but women have duties to perform as mothers."', '"Women,Man,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'An African man should not do anything called housework or cooking.', '"Cooking,Man,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"When I was young we weren\'t even allowed to speak our own languages in school. They called it \'vernacular,\' as if only English was the real tongue."', '"School,Real,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"By the time I finished school, I found out I wasn\'t qualified to study anything but music."', '"Time,Music,School"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Western music is Bach, Handel and Schubert. It\'s good music, cleverly done. As a musician, I can see that."', '"Good,Music,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"The art, the greatness of the music, the experience of the music is what I\'m about. I think most African artists have destroyed their artistry by commercialization, and I don\'t want to belong to that bag."', '"Experience,Art,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"I would never run away from my country. Even at the point of death, I doubt I would move out, because what is the point of leaving your own country?"', '"Death,Country,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'I\'ve studied my culture deeply and I\'m very aware of my tradition.', '"Culture,Tradition,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'I\'m not your average politician. I believe in higher forces.', '"Believe,Politician,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'I\'m playing deep African music.', '"Music,Deep,Playing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"People thought I was trying to say that women had no say, no rights. I was not saying that. I was saying that women had a role, a duty. When they want to have a say in government - though in Africa they are not expected to do that - they are not discouraged. They can do what they want to do."', '"Women,Government,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'My message was \'Think African. Make schools read African history.\'', '"History,Think,Message"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'My music has never been a failure.', '"Failure,Music,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'I think I\'m going to lead my people one day. I\'m sure of it.', '"Day,People,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"My mother was the most wicked mother ever seen in life when it came to beating. Oh-la-la! Every time I would say, \'This is the end of me.\' Oh, how she would beat me."', '"Life,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"It is a false belief to think you can own somebody, I\'m out of that now. The man should understand he does not own the woman, and the woman should understand she does not own the man."', '"Man,Woman,Belief"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Even death doesn\'t worry me, man. When my mother died it was because she finished her time on earth. I know that when I die I\'ll see her again, so how can I fear death?"', '"Death,Time,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Marriage is a terrible institution, it creates such a regression of the mind."', '"Marriage,Mind,Institution"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'Classical music gives musicians a kick. But African music gives everyone a kick.', '"Music,Kick,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Jazz was the beginning of rhythm music, which developed into rock and roll. But what the jazz musicians lost because they were so far from their homeland was the intricate rhythms of African music."', '"Music,Rock And Roll,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'If I became president now I would immediately pass a law that makes every citizen a policeman or a soldier.', '"Law,Soldier,Policeman"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"American record companies seem to feel I am antiwestern, anticapitalism, anti the kind of society they like. They think I\'m a troublemaker."', '"Society,I Am,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'My mother wasn\'t any better than my father.', '"Father,Better,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"It\'s crazy; in the States, people think the black power movement drew inspiration from Africa. All these Americans come over here looking for awareness. They don\'t realize they\'re the ones who\'ve got it over there."', '"Power,Black,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'My country will be a symbol of free human society.', '"Society,Free,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"When I do things, I do things honestly."', '"Things,Honestly"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', 'My ideas are threatening to the government.', '"Government,Ideas,Threatening"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"No, I didn\'t hear about \'Live Aid.\' I was in prison, and we were not allowed newspapers in prison."', '"Prison,Live,Hear"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"Our prisons are very bad. When I was in Ikoyi prison, people were dying every day. They were carrying bodies out of the prison every day."', '"Day,Bad,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0a', '"America needs to hear some good sounds from Africa, man. The sanity of the world is going to be generated from Africa through art."', '"Good,Art,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"The prime goal of censorship is to promote ignorance, whether it is done via lying and bowdlerized school texts or by attacking individual books."', '"Ignorance,School,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"Having a book censored means something. It means you have deeply offended one or more people who felt they needed to protect unsuspecting readers from your inflammatory words, thoughts, and images."', '"Thoughts,Words,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"All writers want to know that someone is reading their work, taking them seriously. It provides a kind of moral support."', '"Work,Support,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"To be censored is one sure way of knowing you have been taken dead seriously. It also speaks to the continuing power of the printed word, almost fifteen hundred years after that amazing invention."', '"Power,Amazing,Dead"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"I\'m an active author: I travel to give readings and talks, although I know it\'s risky."', '"Travel,Know,Active"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', 'I over-scrutinize anyone new entering my life.', '"Life,My Life,New"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', 'I couldn\'t swear that I believed in the law - or in the American legal system.', '"Legal,Law,American"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0c', '"I\'m 68 years old, and I\'m as much a criminal now as I was at the age of 22. And, I\'m even more of a dissident than I was then."', '"Age,Old,More"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Social media is an amazing tool, but it\'s really the face-to-face interaction that makes a long-term impact."', '"Amazing,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Every single job is a challenge. You are walking into a new set, a new character, creating a world and trying to get comfortable to do your best work."', '"Work,Best,Do Your Best"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'Nobody sets out to break new ground. I think change comes when people have no other choice.', '"Change,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"If you know your characters well enough, you aren\'t trying to grasp for storylines. You\'re really thinking about their flaws and their passions and what they\'re chasing."', '"Thinking,Flaws,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I still do commercial work as an actor, which I love, because it\'s very quick, and it definitely pays my bills."', '"Love,Work,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I feel like maybe I\'m part of that generation that became more of a gamer than a video consumer. It\'s always been something I\'ve done with my spare time. If I had three hours on a Friday night, I\'m not out partying. I\'m probably playing video games."', '"Time,Night,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"My dad was in the military, yeah. He was in the Air Force, and he was a doctor, so he would go places for six months here, and two years there. And I was home-schooled because I played the violin, and I did a lot of competitions."', '"Dad,Doctor,Violin"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I think the whole definition of a geek is somebody being passionate and focused, and being proud of saying that they\'re passionate and focused, on a narrow range of subjects."', '"Proud,Saying,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I was a child of a tech family. My grandfather was a nuclear physicist and was always a gadget guy.', '"Family,Always,Child"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I was a huge fan of video games; I wanted to write something, and I saw the tools at my fingertips to upload a video to my audience, and that\'s why I\'m here today. I think that freedom and the lack of gatekeepers, combined with people\'s passion, is what really the true spirit of Internet geekdom is about."', '"Freedom,Today,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Whether you\'re a Twitter follower, a YouTube subscriber or a Facebook friend, natural social instinct is to collect people and to not kind of see them later. But unfortunately, with social media, you collect them and they\'re in your life, whether you really want them or not."', '"Life,Social Media,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I think the more web video there is, the more press you\'ll get, as well as all the people who want to tell stories that haven\'t been told before but can\'t do that on TV because different stories are a risk."', '"People,Tell,More"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'My favorite \'Mister Rogers\' episodes were always the ones where Mr. Rogers would go into the community.', '"Community,Always,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"On Tumblr, I\'m really careful about not following too many things. I enjoy going on there to discover new things more than anywhere else now."', '"New,New Things,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I actually did go through severe depression and anxiety attacks where I couldn\'t sleep for weeks. It was definitely several months of being not myself.', '"Myself,Sleep,Depression"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'m a huge fan of BioWare games. I think they do some of the best character-building. I mean, I have a relationship with Thane from \'Mass Effect\' that is as vivid as any crush that I\'ve had on a TV-show character."', '"Best,Relationship,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Geek and Sundry has an eclectic line-up of shows all targeted around things I love: Comics, Tabletop Games, Books and more."', '"Love,More,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"My goal in creating Geek & Sundry was to create a community based around web video, and we\'ve accomplished that, especially on our budget."', '"Community,Create,Creating"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Now that we\'ve transitioned to more Smart TVs, where people are broadcasting their cable box, I hope that Geek & Sundry is something that people will click on in the future, knowing that they\'re going to get content that they love."', '"Love,Hope,Future"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'ve played pretty much every single-player RPG there is, has been, ever will be. But as far as the MMOs go, especially with the voice chat, it becomes like hanging out with your friends in a chat channel, and you\'re playing at the same time. So it becomes a lot more social than people would probably think."', '"Time,People,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"People always ask why I stay in the online space versus going to TV or film, like most people would do, and the answer is that there\'s opportunity for innovation online - not only innovation in storytelling, but also innovation in how you interact with your audience and that is very fulfilling to me personally."', '"Space,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I have a little obsessive-compulsive personality. You can tell because I played online games for eight hours a day.', '"Personality,Day,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I\'d been in Hollywood for five years before I started writing \'The Guild.\' I worked enough to pay all my bills. So I was very lucky in that respect. Most people don\'t make a living acting.', '"Respect,People,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Every quirky girl doesn\'t have to be the best-friend character. It\'s a very limiting and self-fulfilling prophecy. People only write things that will get green-lit, so they write to those stereotypes."', '"Character,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Just because you have star power and a huge marketing budget, you can see from some professional web series, it doesn\'t equal views."', '"Power,See,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I love sitcoms, and I grew up on sitcoms. That\'s my tasty junk food."', '"Love,Food,Junk Food"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Basically, my socialization as a child didn\'t come from any schooling; it came from being in theater and meeting people online."', '"People,Child,Online"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"When I carve out time to game, it\'s because I rationalize that I \'deserve it,\' so I relish every minute of that 2-3 hour session."', '"Time,Game,Deserve"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'ll be in a series for three or four episodes, but then I\'ll be off the series, and downtime, as an actor, is a little more than most people understand. Most of the time you\'re just sitting around taking coffee with friends."', '"Time,Coffee,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'m very persistent; I know the Internet very well, because I grew up on the Internet. I had Internet when there was just dial-up, and the Internet was my social outlet."', '"Internet,Know,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I\'m a big champion of people doing things outside the system.', '"Champion,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I believe you are never past the point of creating opportunities for yourself.', '"Believe,Yourself,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'Voice acting is very different from live-action. You only have one tool to convey emotion. You can\'t sell a line with a look. It\'s all about your vocal instrument.', '"Look,Voice,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Comic-Con has become more of a pop cultural festival, and to not be included feels like you\'re missing the biggest celebration of the year."', '"More,Missing,Year"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I learned that lack of budget can be overcome by fan passion if you can get your content to the people who like what you do.', '"Passion,People,Overcome"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'The substance of what it means to be a geek is essentially someone who\'s brave enough to love something against judgment. The heart of being a geek is a little bit of rejection.', '"Love,Heart,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"At no point am I ever threatened by people who question who I am, or why I like the things I do, or my legitimacy. Because I know who I am very strongly, and I think that\'s what geek culture can reinforce."', '"Culture,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"For the vlogging channel, I wanted to build the infrastructure and build up all the personalities in a way that felt like weren\'t just forcing the audience to watch everyone we have."', '"Way,Everyone,Build"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I don\'t appeal to everyone well. I appeal to fewer people in a much stronger way. That\'s what fandom is to me, and what creates fans for everything I make."', '"Me,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'ve read every single fantasy novel there is. I mean, I would challenge a lot of people to read more fantasy novels than I have."', '"People,Challenge,Fantasy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I\'m super excited about gaming always. That\'s the thing that I geek out over; those are the vlogs that I\'m surfing if I\'m not already playing a game at night.', '"Night,Game,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '\'TableTop\' is packed with gaming celebrities and independent game creators. This is a huge subculture that really doesn\'t have a vehicle to rally around or educate people with.', '"Game,People,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"When I go to a web video meeting and look around, at least half the show runners are women. And a lot are actors-cum-writers who are frustrated with the situation of being a woman actor in Hollywood and have decided to create their own show."', '"Women,Look,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'d been on \'Buffy\' - that is an amazing community, the Joss Whedon fans."', '"Amazing,Community,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'Sustaining an audience with a web series is an impossible task.', '"Impossible,Task,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I could go off into the wilderness and write fantasy novels for the rest of my life and probably be happy; but I always want to challenge myself.', '"Life,Myself,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I think Hollywood has seen what fandom can do for a project. You can definitely see that when you go to Comic-con.', '"See,Project,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I always enjoyed acting. My aunt was actually an actress.', '"Acting,Always,Actress"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I guess I just always had this idea that I would go to Hollywood. I had the typical \'get up and go\' attitude that you have to have in order to make the brave step into the big city.', '"Attitude,Brave,City"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I came from a dance background, so that\'s what I did my whole teenage years. I was at the dance studio a lot. It just becomes your social scene and part of your life."', '"Life,Dance,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I think every role is always exciting and intimidating. I\'ve never had a role where I wasn\'t intimidated by it.', '"Never,Always,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Surprisingly, I think if you\'re known on the Internet, you\'re probably an introvert."', '"Internet,Think,Introvert"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"People don\'t appreciate that when you\'re on the Internet, it\'s a 24/7 job. Even if you\'re not releasing episodes, your show is living and breathing on the Internet because there\'s a community around it. Ninety percent of the work is after the web series is shot, and you have to constantly maintain your community, because it\'s all you have."', '"Work,Community,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"I\'m in a very fortunate position, in that if I had an idea, and I could do it on a web budget, I could probably get it made; it\'s just a question of finding the time to really develop it, because I don\'t want to make anything that I don\'t believe in 100 percent."', '"Time,Believe,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"That\'s what I love about the Internet. Even if it\'s small-scale and you\'re just posting on a forum, that\'s an uncensored expression. That\'s what I love."', '"Love,Internet,Expression"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I\'m definitely more of a \'think game\' kind of girl. I\'ll read every single dialogue and codex entry and lore entry. I really do love projecting myself and creating my character.', '"Love,Myself,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Finishing games has been something I\'m really proud of, seeing something through to the end."', '"End,Proud,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I created \'The Guild\' because nobody was offering me the roles I thought I could do best at in Hollywood.', '"Best,Me,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I\'m resigned to the fact that the corseted history of America is not as exciting as that of Britain.', '"History,America,Exciting"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"There is definitely a way in which women are raised to be less proactive, less business-oriented, and less willing to jump into creative no man\'s land. I think media has more of an influence on how we perceive gender identity than anything else."', '"Women,Man,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Typecasting is something I have to be careful with, since I play myself on Geek & Sundry so much on my weekly show \'The Flog.\' That\'s why I did \'Dragon Age: Redemption\' last year, so I could do something a little more dramatic and hard-edged."', '"Age,Myself,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"\'The Last Of Us,\' to me, is just amazing storytelling, because everything\'s from the character point of view, which even movies don\'t really do successfully a lot of the time."', '"Time,Amazing,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'That\'s the great thing about incubating something on the web: you have the potential to go to other platforms. Every single platform has a different audience that you find.', '"Great,Find,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"My goal with every show we put on Geek & Sundry is to make it that big of a success, not just within the video but within fandom itself."', '"Success,Big,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"People don\'t teach you how to handle the workload that comes from a little bit of success, and it\'s something I\'d never had to handle, because I\'d been rejected for so long."', '"Success,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', 'I would never let somebody say that they\'re me. That would be the ultimate betrayal of what I stand for.', '"Me,Stand,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"Hollywood typecast me as the secretary. I could have worked as the quirky secretary for the rest of my life, but I decided not to do that."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0d', '"What I love about what I get to do is that I\'m allowed to create the stories that I want to tell with minimal interference by some very big corporations like Microsoft and Sprint and EA and BioWare. The advantage that these tech companies have is that they understand the space organically, versus traditional media companies."', '"Love,Space,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0e', 'Strength is born in the deep silence of long-suffering hearts; not amid joy.', '"Strength,Silence,Joy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0e', '"Gird your hearts with silent fortitude, suffering yet hoping all things."', '"Suffering,Your,Silent"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'A win for one is a win for all - and I\'m not just saying that because Dumas did.', '"Win,Because,Saying"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"The pressure on women to be thin is like a plague. I have gone through my life, like a lot of women, rating my experiences on the basis of, \'Was I thin at that time or fat?\' And it doesn\'t seem to let up."', '"Life,Women,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'Beauty can make you powerful in a way that isn\'t good for you. Being OK is better for the person I have become.', '"Beauty,Good,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'I have six sisters and two beautiful daughters - that\'s eight women who mean the world to me. I support the Entertainment Industry Foundation and Lee National Denim Day because they fund programs that are making huge strides in breast cancer research and support.', '"Women,Beautiful,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"I think I\'ve always had a 40-year-old body, and now that I\'m actually there I\'m like, \'Hey, pretty good, huh?\'"', '"Good,Body,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"Between work and the kids, I never see anyone anymore. I mean, when I first met with ABC last spring, and they asked me what I\'d been doing lately, I said: \'Gee, I have two kids. I\'m usually covered with food, wrinkled and feel guilty all the time."', '"Work,Time,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"I love actors. I married one. OK, I married a fantastic one."', '"Love,OK,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"As you grow up and get educated in the business, you go from, \'I want to do movies\' to \'I want to work. In whatever.\'"', '"Work,Business,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'Motherhood has been an exercise in guilt.', '"Exercise,Guilt,Motherhood"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"The truth is women use contraception not only as a way to prevent unintended pregnancies, but also to improve their health and the health of their families. Increased access to contraception is directly linked to declines in maternal and infant mortality."', '"Health,Truth,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"Right after \'Desperate\' sold to China, we were the most watched show around the world at the time. That\'s really something great to be a part of."', '"Time,Great,World"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'Just let your skin breathe.', '"Skin,Your,Breathe"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"I look OK. I look better in person than I do on film, which is bad because it\'s how I make my living, but I am not a beauty and on balance I am glad."', '"Beauty,Look,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"I can\'t wait to get my face lifted but my husband says, \'No, don\'t do it.\' I think if it makes you feel better, go for it, but it would be nice if it looked good. There are a lot of people out there who are disasters and you think, \'Why did you do that?\'"', '"Good,Face,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"Congress is attempting to eviscerate women\'s health care. Like many women across America, I am outraged."', '"Health,Women,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"By definition, a hearing is an inquiry into many sides of an issue with testimony from various points of views. But mark this: The Republicans did not have a single woman to testify in support of the contraception mandate. That is not a hearing; that is a sham."', '"Support,Woman,Inquiry"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"Thankfully, President Obama has stood firmly behind women\'s health care issues by supporting coverage for contraception and reaffirming commitment to organizations like Planned Parenthood."', '"Health,Women,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'I can\'t tell you what a pleasure it is to just put my hair under a wig cap and slap on a wig that\'s already done. It\'s dress up for your hair!', '"Dress,Hair,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"I was bulimic and anorexic for a while, just hating my body. As an actress, I was never thin enough, never pretty enough. My boobs weren\'t big enough."', '"Body,Never,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', '"It\'s only because I feel like such a philistine spending all that time in hair and makeup that I started to knit. I used to spend that time studying Italian and French. Then after I had two kids, my brain turned to mush and I took up knitting."', '"Time,Brain,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd0f', 'I go to bed when the kids go to bed because I get up when they get up at 5.', '"Bed,Go,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I have such an eclectic taste. I like listening to classical music and pop music.', '"Music,Listening,Taste"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Without sounding too pretentious, I feel my job is almost like becoming a monk or a nun - it\'s a calling."', '"Feel,Job,Monk"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Fashion choices are never arbitrary. Even if you say you don\'t care, that\'s a decision. There\'s something you\'re trying to say."', '"Decision,Care,Choices"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I am definitely romantic, and I love romantic stories - that\'s why I keep making romantic movies."', '"Love,Romantic,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I actually always had short hair as a kid, and it\'s really liberating. I recommend it. It\'s just very easy. I don\'t have to brush it."', '"Hair,Short Hair,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'d love to do more comedy. It\'d just be nice to go into work and not be crying every day. Some broad slapstick would be great. Falling over banana skins would be wonderful.', '"Love,Work,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"With every film that you do, you\'re always so nervous. You feel exposed because you know people will see this eventually. You sort of have to put all that out of your head. What will be will be. But it\'s nerve wracking."', '"Feel,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"But for everyone, I think, there is always a pressure to conform, and I guess as you get older you realize it\'s less interesting to do that. It starts with you, though, saying, \'I know what I like doing and that\'s what I\'m going to do.\'"', '"Pressure,Know,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I love going swimming. I spent a lot of time in North London in summer going to Hampstead Heath and swimming in the ponds there. It\'s so beautiful; we\'re so lucky to have that in London.', '"Love,Time,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"If it\'s something quite low-key then I\'ll often do my own makeup. But for something like a premiere, it\'s good to have a makeup artist because they know what they\'re doing."', '"Good,Low-Key,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"The more you work, the more people can see that you\'re something different from what\'s come before."', '"Work,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'London is my home. I miss my family so much; it\'s hard being away. And I miss salt and vinegar crisps. And Marmite. And good fudge. Oh my God. Clotted cream fudge.', '"Family,God,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I think, as an actor, you\'re always traveling. There\'s a sense of dislocation sometimes from home."', '"Home,Sometimes,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I think that when something happens when you\'re growing up, like a death or divorce, it does open the world slightly because things aren\'t as straightforward."', '"Death,World,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"My grandmother has dementia, and my mother is looking after her as her primary caregiver. Seeing their relationship has had a profound impact, seeing how tough it is for both of them and seeing how the roles change and how my mother has gone from being a daughter to being the mother."', '"Change,Relationship,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'Often the last thing I want to do is stand up in front of 50 cameras on the red carpet. I\'d rather have a cup of hot milk and an early night.', '"Night,Hot,Stand"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m not a huge jewelry fan.', '"Jewelry,Fan,Huge"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I like to jump into different worlds. I\'m attracted to the emotional rollercoaster of acting. Now I\'ve been doing it for so many years, I must rather enjoy it."', '"Acting,Jump,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think it\'s absolutely about time that we have as many female leads as male. It\'s a very exciting time to be an actress.', '"Time,Actress,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When you\'re in the head of the character, you feel less self-conscious. If I was just being me, I would feel so exposed and be like, \'Why is there a huge camera in my face?\' But, when you\'re believing in the person that you\'re playing, you feel protected. It\'s about being true to that person you\'re playing."', '"Character,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It always starts with a script. I like to have plenty of time to read something, and I always like to read a paper copy. I hate reading it on email. I sit down with a script, and want to see how it hits me. It\'s an instinctive process."', '"Time,Hate,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'m a masochist in some ways. I look for things that I think I can\'t do, then, for some bizarre reason, I really want to do them. Maybe one day I\'ll take the easy route."', '"Look,Day,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It was only after university that I said to myself that I had to take the risk and have a serious go at acting. It\'s such a bizarre profession, because you have to be totally tough to deal with all those times when you\'re being turned down, and then really soft in order to access your character\'s emotions."', '"Myself,Character,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"My most treasured item is the brown leather bag that my mum bought me from a little Italian shop for my 21st. It\'s supposed to be a vanity bag, but I use it as a handbag."', '"Me,Bag,Brown"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I make all my decisions by listening to my instinct and then keeping my fingers crossed it will lead to a good place.', '"Good,Listening,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When you\'re a young actor, there\'s this pressure to rush. But I hope to be doing this into my sixties and seventies, so I\'d prefer to take my time."', '"Hope,Time,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"The key is working with great directors. A film is so many different people and all their talents, but particularly the directors, because of the idiosyncrasies of that person."', '"Great,People,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I think you\'re attracted to things that are different from yourself in a character because it\'s more interesting, and you get to play out a fantasy version of yourself."', '"Character,Yourself,Fantasy"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"There\'s so much of a desire in the entertainment industry for newness, a desire to build somebody up and then treat them as old news within six months. I think you\'d be naive if you didn\'t try to hold on to your own way of doing things."', '"Treat,News,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Of everything I have done, \'The Archers\' always gets the most excitement; there\'s a sort of uncontrollable joy from fans of the program."', '"Joy,Fans,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Acting has always existed alongside my normal life. It\'s been a case of learning on the job. I\'ve worked in so many styles, with so many people, so I\'ve picked bits up from everyone and everything."', '"Life,Learning,People"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'m interested in all forms of performance, yet I think it\'s difficult to be as equally talented in all of them as they call for such different skills. At the moment, I still feel I\'m learning and want as much experience and variety as possible."', '"Experience,Learning,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I guess I\'m a bit of a romantic.', '"Romantic,Guess,Bit"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'It can be very intense being an actor; it can be quite a small world. Then you speak to your friend who is a scientist and they have a completely different perspective.', '"World,Perspective,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It\'s nice to have some continuity you can come back to. I feel that in coming home, coming back to London."', '"Home,Feel,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m very excited that I can get on a skateboard and skateboard down the street now. That was something I never thought I\'d be able to do. I conquered my fears.', '"Street,Never,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'m not really massively into going out. I\'m much more of a hibernator. It\'s nice to have people come to your house or go to someone\'s house, I think."', '"People,Someone,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'A lot of my time is spent watching films and reading scripts. And it can be all-consuming. And it\'s obviously something I\'m fortunate that is both my work and my hobby. It\'s what I would naturally be doing anyway.', '"Work,Time,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m attracted to playing people who aren\'t necessarily straightforward.', '"People,Who,Straightforward"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"You have to be brave and not always play likeable people. It\'s difficult, because there\'s a demand for the hero or heroine to be very likeable."', '"Hero,Brave,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I always wear the shoes of the character a week before going on set; the idea of just putting on a new pair of shoes on the first day of filming is just horrific.', '"Character,Shoes,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'m very independent, creatively, always trying to push myself - and I think that comes from my mother."', '"Myself,Independent,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Day to day, I always wear eyeliner on my top lid and mascara. I like to do my own makeup, it depends on the event."', '"Day,Always,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I don\'t like when I look too cluttered.', '"Look,Like,Too"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"You just have to take these opportunities when they come along. They\'re not that frequent; you\'ll get a really good script, oh, maybe once a year if you\'re lucky."', '"Good,Year,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"As a child, I always liked dressing up and getting into character, and actors are lucky in being able to retain that playfulness, though we do seem to find it hard to grow up."', '"Character,Grow,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'ve never done a superhero movie. It\'s very nice to you as an actor in several worlds to go and to experiment.', '"Done,Never,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I don\'t have much time for shopping so I pick things up when I can. My favorite labels are APC, Isabel Marant and Agnes B because the clothes are cut small and have a simplicity to them."', '"Time,Simplicity,Shopping"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I have a great plain blue shirt from APC, and a denim one from Dolce that I wear constantly. It\'s hard to find the perfect denim shirt, but this is it."', '"Great,Perfect,Blue"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I would describe my look as \'ladylike rock chick.\'', '"Look,Rock,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I use SPF every day, then apply foundation, mascara, eyeliner and blusher. I always take my make-up off at night and moisturize."', '"Night,Day,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'There\'s such a sense of theatre in getting glammed up; it\'s like putting on a play or short film.', '"Theatre,Film,Short"', '2023-05-29 11:40:00', '2023-05-29 11:40:00'),
	('390881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'My mother worked in advertising and my father was a journalist. But they split up when I was three and I grew up in a single-parent family. My mum brought my brother and I up.', '"Family,Father,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m more of a freestyle dancer. I like to do my own thing.', '"My Own,Own,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'m used to doing independent film where the style is a lot more casual. With improvising, you obviously find so much out on the day - and in a way, I feel more comfortable doing that."', '"Style,Day,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think human nature is eternal and constant.', '"Nature,Human,Human Nature"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Once you\'re playing someone, you shouldn\'t be judging them in any way. That\'s what being an actor is - it\'s having empathy for people that are different from yourself. Once you\'ve committed to that person, your responsibility is to tell that story."', '"Responsibility,Yourself,Empathy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I am quite fortunate, because I can still be quite incognito. If you go out looking for attention, then you\'ll attract it, but if you\'re just getting on with your life, particularly in London where everyone is engrossed in what they\'re doing, you can keep a measure of anonymity."', '"Life,I Am,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I was a very rotund child with short hair, and for some reason, I always had black ballet shoes. I was like the Wednesday Addams of ballet."', '"Black,Shoes,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It is disheartening when you read an interview with an actress, and it starts by describing what she is wearing."', '"Interview,She,Actress"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think there is an enormous appetite for great roles for women. You can see that clearly with things like \'The Hunger Games.\'', '"Women,Great,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I always think Michelle Williams is excellent in her work. And I do love Sofia Coppola. She always creates something so atmospheric. I love Wes Anderson, Roman Coppola, Andrea Arnold."', '"Love,Work,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I don\'t think my parents would have let me go straight into acting full time when I was 12. I do like to have balance, naturally, as an individual."', '"Time,Me,Balance"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"For everyone, \'Star Wars\' has been a part of their lives in some capacity. I remember watching it very early on with my cousins and my brother, and we were all cuddled around the VHS player, which sounds very old-fashioned, but that was the way then."', '"Remember,Way,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"There\'s so much that goes into a film that I feel like it\'s a bit arrogant to say, \'Oh, I never watch my own movies.\' Well, it\'s not just you. There\'s a whole host of other people. So much skill goes into it. But I would say it does take a couple times seeing it to get a level of perspective."', '"Movies,Skill,Perspective"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Any creative process comes with a level of self-analysis and self-criticism. There\'s a lot of waking up in the middle of the night going, \'Oh, I wish I had done that differently.\'"', '"Night,Process,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"You have to have a bag of Yorkshire Tea bags. It is the best tea that England has to offer, and that comes with me everywhere I go."', '"Best,Me,Bag"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When I come home, I am literally the most popular person with my friends\' parents for doing \'The Archers.\'"', '"Home,I Am,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'ve never done this level of physical preparation for something. Particularly for \'Rogue One\' where I was training every day and doing kung fu rehearsals on a daily basis. But that\'s part of the reason I wanted to do it, because it was very different from what I\'ve done before."', '"Daily,Training,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When I was 11 years old, I was a member of \'Press Pack,\' which was a thing that would come out in \'The Sunday Times\' in England. You\'d write articles and send them off and would get a badge saying \'Official Press.\' I was really excited about my badge."', '"Old,Excited,Saying"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I hardly ever watch the news... I love reading newspapers, but I know they\'re dying out."', '"Love,News,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think that my parents\' divorce gave me a very strong sense of self-reliance and independence. I realised that I needed to make sure I could support myself because you don\'t know what\'s going to happen in the future.', '"Future,Independence,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m a horrible perfectionist and very highly strung. That\'s why I do yoga: to unwind.', '"Unwind,Why,Horrible"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I think actors always find the dialogue doesn\'t quite fit, so you always have to play with it."', '"Always,Find,Dialogue"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"In a way, \'Like Crazy\' keys into our generation, this idea of now we can still be in communication. Where do the boundaries of relationships end?"', '"Communication,Crazy,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"The actresses I\'ve known support each other very much. If you have a level of confidence in what you\'re doing, then you don\'t feel threatened. We all have different things to offer."', '"Confidence,Support,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"A fashion show is like a 10-minute play, but there\'s all this anticipation; Everyone arriving, finding their seats, then there\'s 10 minutes of people walking past and clothes and music, then the whole thing is finished."', '"Music,Past,Walking"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I learnt circus skills in drama group, so I can juggle."', '"Drama,I Can,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m obsessed with subtexts. I love that we often don\'t say what we feel. That gap between the two. I like it when actors reveal a lot without having to say it.', '"Love,Feel,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"In everyday life, I like APC, Isabel Marant, but I also like Zara. It depends how I\'m feeling on the day. I like clothes that have a certain strength to them - simple but graphic."', '"Life,Strength,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Emotional messiness is my reason for life. In acting, it\'s so important."', '"Life,Important,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I love the Spider-Man story. I watched the cartoon on TV when I was a kid, and my brother wore his Spider-Man pyjamas everywhere."', '"Love,Cartoon,Story"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I just took everything so seriously in my early twenties. But now I\'m like, \'life can be fun.\' You don\'t have to overthink everything. I\'ve found a way to be more at peace with things. I\'m looking forward to turning 30."', '"Life,Peace,Looking Forward"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think the writing skills of actors are sometimes underestimated.', '"Sometimes,Writing,Skills"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I love spending time researching a character and reading about them.', '"Love,Time,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Actors and directors work on things together. That\'s how I like to work, anyway. I don\'t want to be told what to do. I want to share it with someone and work it out together."', '"Work,Together,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I\'m happiest when I\'m discussing a script and working with interesting people.', '"People,Interesting,Happiest"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"If you\'re in a film that you\'re proud of and you care about, then you\'re always happy to talk about it."', '"Care,Happy,Proud"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I actually studied literature at university, so I\'m much more of an arts-based person, but I remember I actually did enjoy physics because you got to do weird experiments. I remember we did this thing with static where we all had to put our hands on this static ball to see that your hair would all stand on end."', '"Remember,Hair,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I love French films, and I copy things I see in them. I read magazines and also look at Tumblr. I love nails, so I literally just search the word \'nails\' on Tumblr and start looking."', '"Love,Look,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'My bag always weighs a ton. I carry my whole bathroom with me. You never know what\'s going to happen in a day!', '"Me,Day,Bag"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I always take off my makeup. My mother always told me to do this, and I never go to bed without doing it. I use a good moisturizer and Mario Badescu face wash."', '"Good,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I always love listening to Bob Dylan. \'Blood on the Tracks\' is one of my favorite albums.', '"Love,Listening,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I think we\'re very lucky that there is a tradition of British actors working in America and being respected in America, and I\'ve always liked Kate Winslet and her work and respected her."', '"Work,America,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I love \'Annie Hall\'; I will always come back to that film again and again. Diane Keaton has been such an inspiration to me. She always brings humour, but complexity, and I love watching her on screen. She\'s got real charisma."', '"Love,Me,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I usually have two or three books on the go at the same time. If I\'m in different moods, I want to read different things."', '"Time,Three,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"She was obsessed with French and Swedish cinema. I also remember our mother showing us \'Gone With the Wind\' very early on. She absolutely loved Vivien Leigh, so it must have been a formative experience for me, thinking, \'Oh, maybe one day I\'ll be like Vivien Leigh.\'"', '"Experience,Thinking,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Interviewing someone is very similar to preparing a character, isn\'t it? You\'re just asking questions: \'Who is this person? Why did they make that choice? Why are they doing that?\' You\'re being Sherlock Holmes."', '"Character,Choice,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I always had a very strong sense of independence. I really liked being able to buy my Alanis Morissette \'Jagged Little Pill\' album. I wore that as a badge of honor. I love not having to rely on anyone.', '"Love,Independence,Honor"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"My boy cousins used to sit my older brother and me down and take us through a film-studies course. It included \'Tremors\', \'The Goonies\', and, of course, \'Star Wars\'. That was when it began: sitting cross-legged watching as the opening crawl goes up the screen."', '"Me,Watching,Boy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"My agent called me up and said, \'There is a tremendous female lead in the new \'Star Wars\' film, and I think you\'re really going to like it.\' The opportunity to play someone determined, who\'s trying to find her skills as a leader; to be in a fantasy movie; to be able to do a leading female role in a film of that scale - that\'s very, very rare."', '"Opportunity,Me,New"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'ve always been a feminist, and what I love in my work is being able to explore a full-sided woman and not patronize her."', '"Love,Work,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I did think that acting would be much more like being a pop star. Now I\'m here, I can\'t think of anything more different."', '"Acting,Anything,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I would be writing an essay that was due in the next day until about 1 A.M., and then I would be up at 6 A.M. and on a train to Birmingham to record \'The Archers\'. It was pretty intense."', '"Day,Train,Next"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I don\'t actually think there has ever been too much emphasis on what I am wearing.', '"I Am,Too Much,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I think there is an enormous appetite for great roles for women.', '"Women,Great,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It\'s funny how seeing a love story never gets boring, because it\'s the dream, isn\'t it? It\'s the dream to have a true connection with another human being."', '"Funny,Love,Boring"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"The ideal would be to have a career like Meryl Streep\'s or Kate Winslet\'s. It\'s just unbelievable how they manage to make such incredible choices one after the other. If you could have a career anything like that, then that would be a great thing."', '"Great,Choices,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When you\'re a skateboarder or a snowboarder, it affects the way you talk, the way you move, the way you interact with the world and other people."', '"World,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"On \'Rogue One,\' we had these sets with tiny little buttons that would light up when you pressed them, and screens full of graphics, and it really felt like you were driving a spaceship. The level of detail; you\'ll be two meters away from where the action is, but there\'ll be a little detail there just in case the camera catches it."', '"Light,Action,Camera"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It\'s nice to film in somewhere that you actually love being. Usually, you\'re in a studio for months on end, and you never see any daylight, so you really make the most of it."', '"Love,See,End"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I just always want to play people. I don\'t want it to be necessarily that you relate to the character as female or male, but that you relate to them as a person. That\'s the driving force."', '"Character,People,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'ve heard directing talked about as being a benign dictatorship, and I think that\'s probably the best way a director should be. They\'re open to collaboration and feedback from people, but ultimately, it\'s got to be that one person\'s vision. That\'s what I think makes a film really stand out."', '"Best,Vision,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I was thinking \'Love Story\', obviously, was a romantic film of that time."', '"Love,Time,Romantic"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I was so passionate about wanting the role in \'Like Crazy,\' I filmed myself in the shower because that\'s where one of the scenes was set. It just felt instinctive. It was a close up! It would have been strange if I\'d sent off a wide shot of myself. That\'s not the kind of work I want to do!"', '"Work,Myself,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"It can be frustrating when you\'re put in a category with others. Women do get lumped together in this reductive grouping, and you think, \'Gosh, that rarely happens with the boys.\' I\'m sure people don\'t say to Eddie Redmayne, \'How do you feel about Andrew Garfield?\'"', '"Women,Together,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"The luxury of radio is that you don\'t spend hours in make-up, and you can wear whatever you want. It\'s bizarre. You\'ll be saying lines, with various people around making sound effect noises."', '"People,Radio,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I love being able to change from big films to small films.', '"Love,Change,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I feel like I personally have been lucky.', '"Feel,Lucky,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"If the part isn\'t always there on the page, I\'ve had good relationships with writers where there\'s an openness to bring more to the role."', '"Good,Always,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"When a relationship with a director is really working, you have the same idea at the same time. You go, \'Look, this isn\'t working,\' and they\'ll go, \'I know it\'s not working. What are we gonna do?\' And you go and try something else."', '"Time,Relationship,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '\'Great Expectations\' has become one of my favorite books.', '"Great,Expectations,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I\'d studied English literature at university, but I was also far more enamored with Virginia Woolf, Katherine Mansfield, and James Joyce. That was my passion."', '"Passion,Literature,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"Nothing beats an \'Archers\' fan for their levels of devotion. I think it\'s because it\'s radio, and you obviously conjure up an image of the character that is so powerful."', '"Character,Nothing,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"People keep saying how amazing it is having a female lead, and I just sort of feel, \'Well, of course!\'"', '"Amazing,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"While you are improvising, you need to be prepared, and I like to have a sense of who the character is, what she likes to read, where she grew up, where we went to school, and what she has for breakfast, so that when I go to set, I\'m free to explore."', '"Breakfast,Character,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"I love moments in film where there\'s no dialogue, and somebody communicates something with a look that kills you. That\'s why I love going to the cinema."', '"Love,Look,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"You still slightly down that you\'re ever going to work again, every time you finish something. That\'s the territory of being an actor. It\'s like anything that\'s competitive. It takes a lot of determination. I just feel lucky to be able to do something that I really love."', '"Love,Work,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I actually love doing comedy!', '"Love,Comedy,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', '"My mother was in the kind of late-\'60s, early-\'70s origins of female emancipation. And she was very much like, \'You\'re not going to be defined by how you look. It\'s going to be about who you are and what you do.\'"', '"Look,Mother,She"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd10', 'I want to be paid fairly for the work that I\'m doing. That\'s what every single woman around the world wants. We want to be paid on parity with a man in a similar position.', '"Work,Man,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"Success breeds success, and failure leads to a sort of fallow period."', '"Success,Failure,Leads"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"For me, compatibility is a sense of humour, being able to laugh together; that is very important."', '"Together,Me,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I wouldn\'t trade anything for family time. To me, it is more important than everything else, and I have a very deep-rooted belief in it, which is influenced by my Jewish faith. That\'s a very great source of who I am and what I believe in."', '"Faith,Family,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'I don\'t treasure things much - just people. And pets.', '"People,Treasure,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I don\'t think I\'ve ever not had a dark side. But one of the wonderful reasons why you go into this business is that half your life you live in a fantasy, which is somebody else\'s life. It\'s actually a great release because you\'re not having to deal with the itty-bitty bits of life."', '"Life,Business,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I think very few people do find a relationship where, every moment of every day, everything they do comes together. That\'s why, in a nutshell, everyone loved Barbara in \'The Good Life.\' She was the perfect partner. It was a formula. She wasn\'t glamorous. She wasn\'t clever. But she was a good partner. That\'s too easy, too perfect."', '"Life,Relationship,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'There is the most wonderful thing called Polaris: it\'s a very high frequency laser treatment that lifts and tightens the skin.', '"Skin,Wonderful,High"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"From the early days of the Raj, Shakespeare had been woven into the fabric of India\'s education, and my father understood that in a culture rich with storytelling and fantastical tales, Shakespeare\'s characters and storylines resonated in a powerful way."', '"Education,Culture,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"When I was little I always thought I was marked out, special, on the verge of something momentous. I used to tingle with anticipation."', '"Always,Anticipation,Special"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"As we have more women in power, so the plays and the TV dramas are reflecting what\'s happening."', '"Women,Power,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'Every woman feels she is too old and has missed the boat.', '"Boat,Woman,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I do still get the odd fan letter about The Good Life, clearly written by somebody aged 18, who says: Will you send a photograph? And I think: Maybe it\'s kinder not to. I\'m deeply into my 50s now."', '"Life,Good,Good Life"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I hope to start enjoying flirting again when I\'m 70, like my mother did."', '"Hope,Start,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'I think you have to relax about aging. What else can you do?', '"Relax,Aging,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'I\'m sure people in the business have said: She\'s too old for that part. I don\'t hear about it because your agent protects you from those negative things.', '"Business,Negative,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', 'So many roles for women demand that you make the audience fall in love with you or sympathise with you.', '"Love,Women,Fall"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"The girl-next-door image is a sort of joke; for years, I couldn\'t get any roles other than as somebody dark."', '"Dark,Image,Joke"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"When I was much younger, I sometimes felt rejected by feminists because of an image that I sold because it paid the bills. Any fool could tell my hair is dyed."', '"Fool,Hair,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I haven\'t done fillers or Botox for ages. There comes a point where you have to match bits of you with the other bits; otherwise, you get a terribly random situation."', '"Random,Situation,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"It\'s nice not to have lines when you frown, especially on TV. I don\'t know why people make such a fuss about it. No one is interested if a woman has her teeth capped or her hair dyed."', '"Woman,Hair,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"It\'s difficult to say what attracts one person to another. It\'s always a combination, isn\'t it? I\'ve always found people interesting because of the way they think, and a sense of humour is irresistible."', '"Difficult,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"A lot of my close friends are nothing to do with show business. But the people I\'ve had relationships with, invariably, I\'ve worked with. I think that\'s probably because I grew up in a family where we all worked together, so it\'s something I feel comfortable with."', '"Family,Business,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I love a mask. It\'s why I\'ve got a thing about good writing. When you\'re acting, you\'re going into someone else\'s work. You\'re behind his words; it\'s not you."', '"Love,Work,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I really do believe there are things passed down. Behaviour, not just DNA. Psychological make-up. You can see it in dogs. If you want to breed a calm dog, don\'t get two fighters."', '"Believe,Calm,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I think in the acting world you either manage that transition to older roles, or you stick with what you\'ve always done and then discover nobody can bear you doing it as an older person."', '"World,Done,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"The gym is where I get my chill-out time. I try to go six days a week, but when I\'m working, that goes down to about three."', '"Time,Three,Week"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I love gentle, gorgeous classical music such as Mozart."', '"Love,Music,Gentle"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I did try fillers once. Don\'t ever have fillers because when your cheekbones are high, it\'s chipmunk time."', '"Time,Your,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"My parents were very volatile but very loving. My father would get jealous if my mother looked at somebody. I used to be insanely jealous. It comes out of insecurity. It can come and go, but you get to the point in life where you don\'t have this raging jealousy and protectiveness about your world."', '"Life,Jealousy,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"My father was my trainer, my teacher. He was closer to my sister in the sense that she adored him and he adored her. He was more like my pal. Because of the 13-year gap, I think by the time I came along, it wasn\'t a big deal. I wasn\'t spoilt or cherished, I was just put to work."', '"Work,Time,Teacher"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I don\'t think, until you\'ve actually lost somebody you really love, that you can go through that door that allows you to be grown-up."', '"Love,Lost,Door"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"We take ourselves so seriously moment by moment, but India shows you a sense of eternity. You\'re one little ant on a hill. You\'re part of life, but you\'re not the whole thing."', '"Life,Moment,Hill"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"Looking back, I got the bed I wanted and I lay in it. I didn\'t want to go to America. If you want to join that world, you have to go and live there, and that was something I could not have done. I am very much about family. It doesn\'t matter where I live, but I feel very needful of my people around me. Besides, theatre is my first love."', '"Love,Family,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I can be very difficult if people are not professional, or lazy - or the opposite, which is take themselves too seriously."', '"Difficult,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I am used to looking good. In a way, if I thought I looked like the back end of a bus, I probably wouldn\'t have done \'Strictly Come Dancing\' and gone out there in public."', '"Good,I Am,Looking Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I have to say I am a \'Strictly\' fan, which is why I am in it. I\'ve always watched it for years. I am not an \'X Factor\' fan, and I just think it is a different show. One is about learning something new and having a great time, and the other is rather desperate."', '"Time,Learning,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I\'m not very much of a foodie; I like small amounts of delicious things, but I\'ve never overeaten - I\'d much rather have a glass of wine."', '"Glass,Never,Wine"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I\'m lucky in that I don\'t like sweet things at all. My father loved cakes to such a degree that he kept forcing them down my throat when I was little, and it put me off for life. He had terrible cholesterol, poor thing."', '"Life,Sweet,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"It was in India that I started my acting career, courtesy of my parents, long before I set foot on stage in England. They headed a company of travelling players performing Shakespeare up and down the land."', '"Long,Parents,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('390999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"Every time we moved on, I joined a different class in a different school with different girls until, aged 13, my father had taken the decision to pull me out of school altogether. Everything I needed, he reasoned, could be found within the rich language of Shakespeare\'s plays at which, by then, I was something of an old hand."', '"Time,Decision,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"After making my stage debut aged nine as Macduff\'s small son in \'Macbeth,\' I had played a number of parts, from \'Twelfth Night\'s Viola to \'The Merchant Of Venice\'s Portia\'."', '"Night,Son,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"The problem men seem to have, and women, too, is that they have this very structured idea that we should find a partner and settle down and be, you know, faithful. And yet clearly this is really, really hard for anybody to do!"', '"Women,Men,Partner"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"In a play, the director is God, and I\'m a great arguer. Rather boringly so, I think, about trying different things."', '"God,Great,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd11', '"I don\'t take money seriously, so I can\'t keep any."', '"Money,Seriously,Keep"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'I didn\'t speak much Italian. I did a few courses so I knew a bit before I got there but you have to be there to learn. When I went out for lunch or dinner on my own it was very complicated to order. I spent two months eating the same thing. I always asked for spaghetti carbonara and a fizzy drink. Then I had to diet to lose the weight I gained.', '"Diet,Lunch,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"If an opportunity shows up, or when I present myself at Lazio, I have to present myself very well."', '"Myself,Opportunity,Present"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'If you take your eye off the ball or lose focus for even a minute you can lose a game against any team.', '"Focus,Game,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'My favourite museum is the British Museum.', '"Museum,British,Favourite"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'I have always enjoyed dribbling. That has been a key part of my game and you do get quite a lot of space in England. But the game is very intense and it is difficult to keep it up for the 90 minutes.', '"Space,Game,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"I understand almost everything in English. I am just not 100 per cent on numbers, so when I am out I am comfortable ordering food but when I am paying, I have to make sure I am paying the right amount!"', '"Food,I Am,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'I always dreamed one day to be playing in the Premier League and I am settled here already.', '"I Am,Day,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"I am happy with what I have done until now, but there are things I would like to improve. I would like to do more, there is always margin to grow and reduce mistakes, fix things to get things perfect."', '"I Am Happy,Grow,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"I just want to do my best for the club, win as many titles as possible."', '"Best,Win,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"There were times when we didn\'t have enough food on the table. When it came to the end of the month, I could see my parents were sad because they were unable to give us the best. They had lots of debts. Sometimes they had arguments about it."', '"Best,Sad,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"The Premier League is the best league in the world, and it is very well regarded if you get a chance to play in it."', '"Best,Chance,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'I was the youngest member of my family and I had always been protected but then I had the opportunity to move very far away at the age of 13.', '"Family,Age,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"I do try to get to a new part of London every week, visit a museum once or twice a week if possible."', '"New,Week,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', '"It\'s certainly been very important to have my own family with me. They came with me to Italy, left what they had in Brazil and also adapted to a new country, new culture and new language was difficult but having their support in the good and bad times was fantastic."', '"Family,Good,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd12', 'Every player dreams of playing for a team like United.', '"Dreams,Like,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Positive things come out of even the most difficult times.', '"Positive,Difficult,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Mercedes for me is the strongest team.', '"Me,Mercedes,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Sometimes in the difficult moments in you life you learn more, you grow up more."', '"Life,Grow,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"For sure working with Ferrari is a great pleasure. It\'s a great team, it\'s a great experience and it\'s a great dream as well to be there."', '"Experience,Great,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I retired in Formula One and I think it was the right time, so I\'m happy with my decision."', '"Time,Decision,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I already lived in Switzerland in 2002, and from this time I know that it\'s a very calm country. I really enjoy living there."', '"Time,Calm,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I love watches, for sure. The watch I love the most is Richard Mille because it\'s part of something that started from zero."', '"Love,Watches,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When I entered Formula One in 2002 basically all I had was my talent, but now I also have the technical knowledge which enables me, together with my engineers, to fully exploit the potential of the car."', '"Car,Knowledge,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"If I had my accident maybe 10 years ago I wouldn\'t be here now. The technology we have now, the helmets, can save your life."', '"Life,Technology,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"That is something you can never explain, it is part of all sporting life. Anybody can have a bad day and they can have many good days."', '"Life,Good,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Playing dirty has never been part of my game.', '"Game,Dirty,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I am not really a problem personality.', '"Personality,I Am,Problem"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'My mother never watches the start of my races - because she fears for me.', '"Me,Start,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When I woke up I didn\'t know why I was in hospital so I was asking \'Why am I here?\' I was pulling all the tubes and my brother Eduardo tried to stop me so we had a fight. The accident was just so unlucky, but I know I am lucky to be alive."', '"Fight,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I think what makes things interesting in Formula E, and I really hope it happens with me, is that many drivers are able to win the race. Maybe many drivers can win the championship."', '"Hope,Me,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"If you are a great guy with your competitors, with your colleagues, it is always good, even on the race track and off it."', '"Good,Great,Colleagues"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I still wanted to race in Formula One, for a correct team, a nice team, one that is professional, where you would feel important. But there was no position for me to carry on, so I felt if that opportunity wasn\'t there, then it would be better for me to stop, and start thinking about doing different things."', '"Opportunity,Thinking,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Since he sold his team, Eddie Jordan has had nothing to do with F1 except for what he says in the press!"', '"Nothing,F1,He"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"After your time passes at Ferrari, you may drive for another team, but you\'re always a Ferrari driver."', '"Time,Drive,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'My dream is always to win the championship and I will keep fighting to achieve what I want.', '"Fighting,Win,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Everything for us as a driver is related to our working, on your work and how you feel. It helps how you feel, how happy you are; also for your private life."', '"Life,Work,Private Life"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I talked to everyone. But I also did work with a professional psychologist, sporting psychologist. That was just the beginning. After that I was able to change the direction to think, the direction to work and I think it was like training I did."', '"Change,Work,Training"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"If you know how to set up the car, if you know how to work with the team, you know what you need to have a comfortable car to drive."', '"Work,Car,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I really believe that if you deserve something then one day you will get it.', '"Believe,Day,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I always respect my team and my competitors. I never had problems with anybody.', '"Respect,Problems,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I\'m not the kind of guy who will blame other people if things don\'t work out.', '"Work,People,Blame"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Sauber had a bad championship the year after they fired me and so if I had stayed it would have not been so good. Sometimes life does these things to you because it\'s the right thing. You think it\'s wrong, \'initially, but life proves different."', '"Life,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'If I don\'t drive then I am not the same person. Ever since I was a small boy this is my life.', '"Life,Drive,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Everything in life has a meaning. If something bad happens it\'s because you need to learn, to grow."', '"Life,Grow,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"What I\'m really trying to do is make karting important like it is. I mean, karting is our sport, this should be really important."', '"Important,Trying,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Honestly, I think they need to work to improve the categories. If the driver goes from the go-kart to F3 one year and then to F1, why do we have GP3, GP2?"', '"Work,Why,F1"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'When you\'re not winning it\'s easy to complain!', '"Winning,Easy,Complain"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I feel competitive all the time I\'m in the car.', '"Car,Time,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"A team that can build a stronger car, a stronger working environment. A team that has the possibility to create something, that would be interesting."', '"Car,Stronger,Create"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I am happy to start from zero, to create, to restart."', '"I Am Happy,I Am,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"My son understands a lot and he\'s pushing me really hard. He always tells me \'you need to win, you need to be good.\' He\'s happy to see that his father is racing and I think he understands step by step more about Formula One and he really likes it."', '"Good,Me,Step"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Ferrari is very political, at Ferrari everything is difficult. So if you win you have a lot of pressure and if you don\'t win you have even more."', '"Political,Difficult,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I don\'t see myself as a leader, I just feel that everything I say, people are listening and people are doing."', '"Myself,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"My family is important to me. They have always been close to me during my career, victories and defeats, and the most difficult moments."', '"Family,Me,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"The accident did not change my life, change the way I think, the way I work. For sure, it gave me even more experience. The biggest problem was my sight, I couldn\'t see with my left eye."', '"Life,Change,Work"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I was sure after the accident when in hospital in Hungary that I was not in the position not to lose any races.', '"Lose,Hospital,Position"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Everything can change pretty quickly in Formula One in two or three races.', '"Change,Three,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'It is important to work to get the good result. If you have that nothing else is important.', '"Work,Good,Result"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I enjoyed my first season with Sauber, for sure."', '"First,Enjoyed,Sure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"It\'s jewelry for men, so definitely it\'s very nice to have a good watch on your wrist."', '"Good,Men,Jewelry"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I have some old cars, but I have some modern cars as well. And I have some race cars, the cars that I race. I have some Ferraris."', '"Race,Old,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'If I don\'t get a race deal then I expect to be a test driver for a top team.', '"Race,Test,Top"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I\'m very confident about being on the grid in Australia in 2003.', '"Australia,About,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'My year with Ferrari was of incredible value to me. I learned a lot about all the technical aspects of the car and also how to improve my work with the engineers.', '"Work,Car,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"With all the traveling I\'m doing, it\'s really important for me to be able to relax when I\'m at home."', '"Home,Relax,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"On the one hand, I set my goals high, but on the other I do not underestimate our competitors either, who are using all their resources to challenge us. However, I also see what a fantastic job Sauber is doing and the progress we are constantly making."', '"Progress,Goals,Underestimate"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I know I am lucky to be alive - but I will race again.', '"I Am,Alive,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I\'m pretty relaxed, trying to enjoy the races, trying to do the best I can in the car, trying to the give the best to the team, and that\'s the most important thing."', '"Best,Car,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"The worst feeling is when you don\'t have brakes, you cannot stop the car and you see that the wall is just coming in front of you. That\'s really a very scary moment."', '"Car,Moment,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"These days it is not very easy to overtake in Formula One, the cars have great aerodynamic downforce. When you are behind a car, you lose downforce."', '"Car,Great,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I was always interested in maybe being in Formula E as I said many times when I was still racing in F1.', '"Always,F1,Racing"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When you\'re talking about proper competition, I think Formula E has good competition."', '"Good,Competition,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'That\'s the only difference in Formula E from other championships - it\'s more unpredictable.', '"Unpredictable,Difference,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"My goal is to be competitive, the best as I can give. My goal never changes in whole my career."', '"Best,Never,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"For sure people around me, they always say don\'t do ovals, we are not happy to see you doing that. I\'m not saying I\'m scared, I\'m not scared to do ovals. But I never thought about it. I was not really planning to go to do Formula Indy."', '"Me,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"The Italians - they cannot talk without shaking the hands. And I am like that, I\'m from Brazil as well."', '"I Am,Hands,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I\'m a big supporter of safety.', '"Safety,Big,Supporter"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I don\'t think really we need to race in F1 just to risk your life, or to be in danger is nice for the people. I don\'t think it\'s really like that."', '"Life,People,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I don\'t want to be the king, \'I don\'t need that, I want to race even without the helmet, I am the king.\' I am not like that. I just want to make things better for the drivers and for the safety."', '"King,I Am,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Every day you are in the media for good or for bad and sometimes this is not helping the driver or the team to control the driver in the best way as well. But Ferrari is Ferrari and the biggest, most famous team in Formula One, so you have a lot more pressure there than at another team."', '"Best,Good,Famous"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When I got to Ferrari I learnt to be less aggressive, and how to set up the car for my driving style."', '"Car,Style,Aggressive"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"The people in the grandstand just want to see good driving, good overtaking. But inside the sport everything is about money and politics. It\'s stupid. And I\'m not just talking about Formula One. It\'s every sport."', '"Politics,Money,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When you\'re at Ferrari, you know your team-mate will be strong."', '"Be Strong,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Sometimes you don\'t see the result that you expect.', '"Result,Sometimes,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"The time I say that I am a number two driver, I will not race any more."', '"Time,I Am,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I will do everything I can always for my country.', '"Country,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"For me, my country is the most important thing."', '"Me,Country,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I am not here really just to race. I am here to win. That\'s really my point.', '"I Am,Win,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Driving for Ferrari is completely different. Not in the way you work, the way of working is similar in whatever team you go - especially in the top teams. But it\'s different because it\'s like a religion."', '"Work,Religion,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I\'m very happy to be joining the Venturi Formula E Team and the Formula E championship, which has become a magnificent competition in such a short space of time."', '"Space,Time,Competition"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"There are a lot of good cars, good teams and good drivers."', '"Good,Lot,Teams"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'A lot of things happen in a difficult way inside Ferrari in terms of pressure.', '"Difficult,Way,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"We had many years with refueling in Formula 1 and we had a few problems, but not really very dangerous problems to be honest."', '"Problems,Dangerous,Formula"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'We always need to keep working to improve safety - not just the cars; the tracks and everything are very safe now.', '"Safe,Safety,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I want to find a team that can give me a competitive car to win many more races and challenge for the championship.', '"Car,Me,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I want to keep having fun like I have done all my life.', '"Life,Fun,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I always had a good relationship with all my team-mates in my career.', '"Relationship,Good,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Many Formula One races last two hours, are really boring and nothing happens."', '"Boring,Nothing,Formula One"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I know how to lose and I know how to win.', '"Lose,Win,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Sometimes things don\'t happen in the way you want it to. But that\'s sport.', '"Way,Sometimes,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I think that if you are well-accepted by the other drivers and respected it is important.', '"Important,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I have a passion for racing, for competing and for fighting on the track."', '"Passion,Fighting,Racing"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"My return is not about seeing Formula One as the best option, but is about seeing the role at Williams as the best option. I would not have returned for any other team."', '"Best,Formula One,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"When the media began reporting that I might return, I was touched by the response from so many fans who wanted to see me back in the sport. That was certainly a factor in the decision, so I\'d like to thank the fans for their support. But, at the end of the day, when I received the call it was an offer I couldn\'t refuse. It was Williams!"', '"End Of The Day,Decision,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"I have zero pressure, because I have nothing to lose."', '"Lose,Pressure,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"My first year, I was really a kind of a wild guy. But I had a very difficult car to drive and I was very young. I think I was maybe too young to have started straight away."', '"Car,Drive,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"People always put me completely out of the game, and that\'s even nicer because nobody expects you to do a good job and then you do a better job than everybody thinks and it\'s nicer."', '"Good,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'Maybe I am the driver who got the most close to the championship in history.', '"History,I Am,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I have zero frustration in my life and that\'s the way it is.', '"Life,My Life,Frustration"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"We are not here for political reasons, we are here for sport, to fight for positions. That\'s the good thing about Formula One."', '"Good,Fight,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'There\'s no better place to be on the podium than here at Monza.', '"Better,Place,Better Place"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', '"Just competing in the Brazilian GP is a dream for all Brazilian racing drivers. I remember sitting in the grandstands when I was a kid, watching Ayrton Senna, Nelson Piquet and even Rubens Barrichello. After that, to race there in Formula One is a feeling that is hard to explain."', '"Remember,Watching,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I\'d like to be remembered as an important component of the Ferrari team.', '"Important,Remembered,Ferrari"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'I am proud to be part of Ferrari\'s history.', '"History,I Am,Proud"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd13', 'It was always my dream to drive for Ferrari.', '"Drive,Always,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"The crown must constantly earn citizens\' appreciation, respect and trust."', '"Respect,Trust,Appreciation"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'The men and women of my generation are heirs to that great collective success which has been admired worldwide and of which we are so proud. It is now up to us to pass it on to the coming generations.', '"Success,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"We have a great country, we are a great nation - let us trust in it."', '"Trust,Great,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'We must never relent in our efforts to resolve conflicts through diplomacy and through all of the instruments bestowed by the Charter of the United Nations.', '"Diplomacy,Never,United Nations"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"In a unified and diverse Spain, based on the equality of and solidarity between its people, there is room for all of us. And for all of our feelings and sensitivities and our distinct ways of being Spaniards."', '"Equality,Feelings,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"I begin my reign with profound emotion at the honour of accepting the Crown, aware of the responsibility it entails and with the greatest hope for the future of Spain."', '"Hope,Future,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'We all have our place in this diverse Spain.', '"Place,Our,Spain"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"Today, more than ever, citizens demand with good reason that moral and ethical principles be upheld and that exemplariness preside over our public life. And the king, as the head of state, must not only be an example but also a servant to that just and legitimate demand of the citizens."', '"Life,Good,Today"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"I want to reaffirm, as king, my faith in the unity of Spain."', '"Faith,King,Unity"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'We mustn\'t hesitate to cut corruption at its roots.', '"Corruption,Roots,Hesitate"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"Together, for over 50 years, King Juan Carlos and Queen Sofia have devoted themselves to Spain."', '"King,Together,Queen"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"Spain and the United States share the same values of democracy, liberty and fundamental freedoms."', '"Democracy,Liberty,Values"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'There must not be favoured treatment for those occupying a position of public responsibility.', '"Responsibility,Position,Treatment"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'Millions of Spaniards have Catalonia in their hearts.', '"Hearts,Millions"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"Our primary objective must be to prevent wars, and when we fail in this, we must protect and assist the innocent victims."', '"Innocent,Protect,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'Public office must not be a means to profit or become rich.', '"Rich,Profit,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', '"You will find in me a loyal head of state who is ready listen and understand, warn and advise as well as to defend the public interest at all times."', '"Me,Will,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'I embody the renewed monarchy for a new time.', '"Time,New,Monarchy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'It is possible for political forces to agree.', '"Political,Possible,Agree"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd14', 'Sincere and generous collaboration is the best way to fulfil the legitimate aspirations of each person and achieve great collective goals for the common good and the general interest.', '"Best,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Love is the expansion of two natures in such fashion that each include the other, each is enriched by the other."', '"Love,Love Is,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"The hero is one who kindles a great light in the world, who sets up blazing torches in the dark streets of life for men to see by."', '"Life,Men,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'Love of country is like love of woman - he loves her best who seeks to bestow on her the highest good.', '"Love,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Where the roots of private virtue are diseased, the fruit of public probity cannot but be corrupt."', '"Fruit,Roots,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'The family is the school of duties - founded on love.', '"Love,Family,School"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"An anxious unrest, a fierce craving desire for gain has taken possession of the commercial world, and in instances no longer rare the most precious and permanent goods of human life have been madly sacrificed in the interests of momentary enrichment."', '"Life,World,Fierce"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Ethical religion can be real only to those who are engaged in ceaseless efforts at moral improvement. By moving upward we acquire faith in an upward movement, without limit."', '"Faith,Religion,Improvement"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'Simplicity should not be identified with bareness.', '"Simplicity,Should,Identified"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"The freedom of thought is a sacred right of every individual man, and diversity will continue to increase with the progress, refinement, and differentiation of the human intellect."', '"Freedom,Progress,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Every dogma, every philosophic or theological creed, was at its inception a statement in terms of the intellect of a certain inner experience."', '"Experience,Statement,Intellect"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'The platform of an Ethical Society is itself the altar; the address must be the fire that burns thereon.', '"Society,Fire,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'No religion can long continue to maintain its purity when the church becomes the subservient vassal of the state.', '"Religion,Long,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"In a country of such recent civilization as ours, whose almost limitless treasures of material wealth invite the risks of capital and the industry of labor, it is but natural that material interests should absorb the attention of the people to a degree elsewhere unknown."', '"Risks,Wealth,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"The past speaks to us in a thousand voices, warning and comforting, animating and stirring to action."', '"Action,Past,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'The exercises of our meeting are to be simple and devoid of all ceremonial and formalism.', '"Simple,Our,Meeting"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"You do not build your own houses, nor make your own garments, nor bake your own bread, simply because you know that if you were to attempt all these things they would all be more or less ill done."', '"Done,Know,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"FOR a long time the conviction has been dimly felt in the community that, without prejudice to existing institutions, the legal day of weekly rest might be employed to advantage for purposes affecting the general good."', '"Time,Good,Legal"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Few are there that will leave the secure seclusion of the scholar\'s life, the peaceful walks of literature and learning, to stand out a target for the criticism of unkind and hostile minds."', '"Life,Learning,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"The ethical manifold, conceived of as unified, furnishes, or rather is, the ideal of the whole."', '"Ideal,Rather,Ethical"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'The office of the public teacher is an unenviable and thankless one.', '"Teacher,Office,Public"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'We measure our enjoyments by the sum expended.', '"Measure,Sum,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"The Ethical Society, therefore, is like a Church in maintaining, and emphasizing the importance of maintaining the custom of public assemblies on Sunday."', '"Society,Church,Importance"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Perhaps a hundred people assembled one evening, May 15, 1876, at the time when the country was celebrating the hundredth anniversary of its political independence."', '"Time,Anniversary,Independence"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"No one can fail to see that the power of the Church among large numbers in many communities is today diminishing, or has already ceased."', '"Power,Today,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"If you desire information on some point of law, you are not likely to ponder over the ponderous tomes of legal writers in order to obtain the knowledge you seek, by your own unaided efforts."', '"Knowledge,Legal,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', 'For more than three thousand years men have quarreled concerning the formulas of their faith.', '"Faith,Men,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd15', '"Admitting the force of these contentions, nevertheless, the custom of meeting together in public assembly for the consideration of the most serious, the most exalted topics of human interest is too vitally precious to be lost."', '"Together,Lost,Serious"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'Sometimes you have to go up really high to understand how small you really are.', '"Sometimes,Understand,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"If the Wright brothers hadn\'t put their lives on the line, we would not be flying around the world these days. So we need pioneers."', '"World,Need,Flying"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I\'m 100 percent sure I\'m becoming a really good helicopter pilot.', '"Good,Pilot,Percent"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I\'m now a member of a pretty small club.', '"Small,Club,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'To jump and break the sound barrier will not be a mere record breaking experience or another extreme event that ends once the mission is accomplished.', '"Experience,Will,Mission"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I base jumped off the Jesus statue in Rio de Janeiro.', '"Statue,Base,Off"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'Heroes don\'t wear diapers. It\'s just not cool.', '"Cool,Heroes,Wear"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"Let me tell you - when I was standing there on top of the world, you become so humble. You don\'t think about breaking records anymore, you don\'t think about gaining scientific data - the only thing that you want is to come back alive."', '"Humble,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I started skydiving because I loved the idea of freedom.', '"Freedom,Loved,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I always feel the danger because you might always be subject to an unexpected or emergency event.', '"Unexpected,Feel,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"Aviation - and space travel, in particular - have always been especially captivating."', '"Space,Travel,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I\'m more a competitive person.', '"Person,More,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"At a certain R.P.M., there\'s only one way for blood to leave your body, and that\'s through your eyeballs. That means you\'re dead."', '"Dead,Body,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I like to challenge myself.', '"Myself,Challenge,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'They call me Fearless Felix.', '"Me,Fearless,Call"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"Normally, when I skydive, even in winter, I wear very thin gloves. I want to be flexible, with fast reactions."', '"Fast,Wear,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'This claustrophobia was the only weakness I had. It\'s not my fault. It\'s just in my mind.', '"Mind,Weakness,Fault"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I feel comfortable with what I do and I guess that my girlfriend feels the same.', '"Feel,Comfortable,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"Well, I jumped for the first time when I was 16. I just loved it and immediately realized that it was what I wanted to do."', '"Time,First Time,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"As a little kid, I climbed a lot of trees because I always loved the bird\'s-eye view."', '"View,Always,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I have a lot of fears that normal people have.', '"People,Normal,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I had to work with a psychiatrist.', '"Work,Psychiatrist,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"If I do something, it\'s always 90% obvious and 10% unknown."', '"Always,Unknown,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I\'m retired from the daredevil business.', '"Business,Daredevil,Retired"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I want to find a nice decent job as a helicopter pilot.', '"Find,Pilot,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I don\'t like to rate myself; others can do that.', '"Myself,Others,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'People are fascinated about the world above them because it seems so out-of-reach.', '"World,People,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I can\'t bear the thought of my mother having to push me around in a wheelchair. I\'d rather die quickly.', '"Me,Die,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I have no privacy anymore.', '"Privacy,Anymore"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'People should decide \'are you willing to spend all this money to go to Mars?\' I think the average person on the ground would never spend that amount of money - they have to spend it on something that makes sense and this is definitely saving our planet.', '"Money,People,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"You have seen on TV how hard it is to go up 129,000 feet and how hard it is to come down."', '"Feet,Hard,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'Of course my life has changed because now everybody knows who Felix Baumgartner is.', '"Life,My Life,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"I always had the dream of flying, and the cheapest way is to become a skydiver."', '"Way,Always,Flying"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I base jumped off one of the highest buildings in the world.', '"World,Buildings,Base"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'I was crossing the English Channel with a carbon-fiber wing on my back.', '"Back,English,Channel"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"I\'ve done a lot of things in a business where you\'re lucky to stay alive, so when the time comes, I\'ll be happy to pass my knowledge along and help someone else."', '"Knowledge,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', 'The stratosphere is a hostile place.', '"Place,Hostile,Stratosphere"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd16', '"Well, to me, my past accomplishments weren\'t crazy. They required a lot of skill and careful planning."', '"Me,Skill,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', '"Thanking you once more, I want to wish you the best of luck for your future life and to conclude by saying to you: Dream your dreams and may they come true!"', '"Life,Dreams,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', 'In talking to you I feel very much more at ease than my colleagues who gave the speeches during the banquet.', '"Colleagues,Feel,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', 'It is inevitable that many ideas of the young mind will later have to give way to the hard realities of life.', '"Life,Mind,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', 'It seems that this situation is not restricted to science but is more generally human.', '"Science,Situation,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', '"Instead of explaining the sober facts of mechanics and electricity, I want to say a few words about the debt which we owe to youth; and with your permission I shall consider you as representing here not only the academic youth of Sweden nor even of Europe but also of America."', '"Youth,Words,Facts"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', '"But these realities will make themselves felt soon enough and while I am certainly not asking you to close your eyes to the experiences of earlier generations, I want to advise you not to conform too soon and to resist the pressure of practical necessity."', '"Eyes,I Am,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', 'Free imagination is the inestimable prerogative of youth and it must be cherished and guarded as a treasure.', '"Imagination,Youth,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd17', 'I am sure my fellow-scientists will agree with me if I say that whatever we were able to achieve in our later years had its origin in the experiences of our youth and in the hopes and wishes which were formed before and during our time as students.', '"Education,Time,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd20', '"Well, it was one of my most gratifying experiences because I could devote my knowledge and my talent for the good for the City of Washington, and all the Federal projects where the Fine Arts Commission had jurisdiction, and it was a tremendous experience."', '"Knowledge,Experience,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd20', 'The early expression of my youth was filled with all the aspects of art.', '"Art,Youth,Expression"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd20', '"I finished my studies in England, I opened my studio in London, and the first one-man exhibit I had on Bond Street, which was opened by the Austrian ambassador."', '"Bond,Street,Ambassador"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Making money is certainly the one addiction I cannot shake.', '"Money,Making Money,Addiction"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'You\'ll never get rich by working for your boss.', '"Boss,Rich,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"America is an empire. I hope you know that now. All empires, by definition, are bumbling, shambolic, bullying, bureaucratic affairs, as certain of the rightness of their cause in infancy, as they are corrupted by power in their dotage."', '"Hope,Power,Bullying"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Money is power. Power is an aphrodisiac.', '"Money,Power,Aphrodisiac"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'No woman or girl is going to want to spend time looking at pretty dresses on the Internet. Vogue is going to be around for a long time to come.', '"Time,Long,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"\'Great Expectations\' has been described as \'Dickens\'s harshest indictment of society.\' Which it is. After all, it\'s about money. About not having enough money; about the fever of the getting of money; about having too much money; about the taint of money."', '"Money,Great,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Nobody could like Donald Trump, surely, except his mother. No one really likes The Donald. But how can you not have respect for a guy who\'s been down on the floor and just keeps coming back? Nothing will keep Donald Trump down until they drive a wooden stake in his heart and a silver bullet in his brain."', '"Respect,Heart,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'What is negotiation but the accumulation of small lies leading to advantage?', '"Negotiation,Small,Lies"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"You have to persuade yourself that you absolutely don\'t care what happens. If you don\'t care, you\'ve won. I absolutely promise you, in every serious negotiation, the man or woman who doesn\'t care is going to win."', '"Man,Yourself,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The reason I don\'t carry a mobile phone is I don\'t want people to know where I am!', '"I Am,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I loathe and detest movies and television and don\'t watch any. I do not have the time.', '"Time,Movies,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Overhead will eat you alive if not constantly viewed as a parasite to be exterminated. Never mind the bleating of those you employ. Hold out until mutiny is imminent before employing even a single additional member of staff. More startups are wrecked by overstaffing than by any other cause, bar failure to monitor cash flow."', '"Failure,Mind,Alive"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I write about whatever turns up. Every single day, I\'m sitting down for three to five hours in the evenings wrestling away and producing far too much verse."', '"Day,Three,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I don\'t take investment advice from wealth managers. I have grown several businesses from scratch and amassed many millions from my publishing empire - why would I take advice from someone who has never experienced that?', '"Advice,Wealth,Investment"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I\'m so suspicious of our own understanding of the past. I just think that your mind plays absolute tricks on you and fools you every minute of every day. And so when you\'re talking about the past, you\'re talking about something that never happened. At least it didn\'t happen the way you think it happened."', '"Mind,Day,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"When I see something that\'s wrong, I just speak and act first and I\'ll take the consequences later."', '"See,Speak,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"With the greatest of respect, I have watched Apple from the day it started. I was publishing magazines about the Apple II before most people had ever heard what a personal computer was."', '"Respect,Day,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Obviously, waste disposal is an enormous and fantastic industry."', '"Industry,Waste,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Native trees are so important to our ecosystem.', '"Important,Trees,Native"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I have an over-attachment to precision, which is why I\'ve sold more magazines than any man alive."', '"Man,Alive,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"You can collect all the plastic bottle caps you want as long as you give me the money so we can get off this death trap, find somewhere else and have tremendous fun screwing that up as well."', '"Death,Money,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"There is never a time in a company\'s history when cost control can be relegated to the back burner, but for a startup company, keeping costs low is a vital necessity."', '"History,Time,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"There are as many forms of happiness as sorrow, though most prove fleeting."', '"Happiness,Sorrow,Prove"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The vast majority of free verse is ghastly. Utterly ghastly. No one reads it. No one listens to it.', '"Free,Majority,Listens"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"This modern mania for interfering in other\'s lives, usually under the guise of health and safety concerns, is highly irritating and counterproductive. Down with the nanny state."', '"Health,Safety,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'It\'s kind of a crazy thing to decide that you\'re going to be worth tens and tens and tens of millions of dollars and set out to do that. It doesn\'t suit everybody.', '"Crazy,Worth,Decide"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I think having a great idea is vastly overrated. I know it sounds kind of crazy and counterintuitive. I don\'t think it matters what the idea is, almost. You need great execution."', '"Great,Crazy,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"You shouldn\'t go around the world behaving ruthlessly when you don\'t have to. Sometimes you do have to. There is only so much pie to go around. If you\'re going to take more than your fair share of pie, as socialists would look at it, then someone else is not getting his. That means you\'ve got to take it away from them."', '"Look,World,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I couldn\'t care less what anyone\'s \'perception\' of me is. I\'m too long in the tooth to care.', '"Me,Long,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Discourse has ended in America. It\'s all just shouting and ranting and demonization. Do you know how the rest of the world laughs at you guys? Have you got any idea? They\'re just rocking with laughter night and day.', '"Laughter,Night,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I\'m very proud of the fact that I\'m one of Britain\'s biggest selling poets. That gives me a huge amount of pleasure.', '"Me,Proud,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Publishing magazines for yourself is not good business, man."', '"Business,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"\'The Week\' is my favourite magazine. Everyone from presidents to CEOs of companies love it, politicians, people in the massive charity business in America, in the arts and even more especially in the media."', '"Love,Business,America"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'You don\'t have to live in a garage to write great poetry.', '"Poetry,Great,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The age of celebrity editors and monstrous staffing are over.', '"Age,Celebrity,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I love the business of business; I love the risk raking.', '"Love,Business,Risk"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Human beings are definitely changing the planet, but how much impact they are having on climate, I don\'t know and I don\'t care."', '"Care,Impact,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"It\'s a long, slow sunset for ink-on-paper magazines, but sunsets can produce vast sums of money."', '"Money,Long,Slow"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I have been portrayed by actors in three television documentaries, two plays, one musical and a film. It\'s no fun watching yourself being traduced and imitated by an actor."', '"Yourself,Fun,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I want to prove that if you write in strict meter and rhyme about subjects people care about, they will buy poetry."', '"Poetry,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I am absolutely convinced that my life was redeemed by poetry.', '"Life,Poetry,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'You cannot be seeking yourself when you\'re making money.', '"Money,Yourself,Making Money"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"No poetry that I\'m aware of, however bad or glorious, has ever left somebody a worse person than they were before they read it."', '"Poetry,Bad,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I cannot abide being bored.', '"Bored,Cannot,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"There are far too many people in university in Britain. If you want to make money, be a plumber."', '"Money,People,Far"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'People who get trapped in the tunnel vision of making money think that is all there is to life.', '"Life,Money,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"With a poetry book I can send 100 copies out to reviewers and other people, and even do it in advance and get their response. It\'s difficult with iPad: how do you send it out for free, and how do you even disseminate it before it goes into their store?"', '"Poetry,Free,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I\'m an entrepreneur, a businessman. I\'ve got a lot of money, and that doesn\'t go very well with the whole \'starving artist in a garret\' routine."', '"Money,Routine,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"People think I\'m just an old Luddite, but that\'s untrue. I buy every new gizmo as it comes out, play with it until I understand how it works, and then give it away."', '"New,People,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"For me, temptation is life and I have a gargantuan appetite for everything."', '"Life,Me,Temptation"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I am a born-again atheist, so there isn\'t going to be a funeral. I will be buried in a linen wrap in a cardboard coffin in my forest with an oak tree planted on my head."', '"I Am,Tree,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"When I was young, I wanted to be the greatest blues singer of all time. I wrecked my education and left home for it."', '"Education,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The best thing about being immensely wealthy is not having to be in any particular place at any particular time doing a particular task you don\'t want to do.', '"Best,Time,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The beginnings of a forest is one of the ugliest things on the planet. It\'s bleak and your neighbours hate you.', '"Hate,Forest,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I thoroughly object to getting old. If you could let me be 16 again, I\'d give you everything I\'ve got and everything I\'ll ever have."', '"Me,Everything,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I never sue journalists. I employ journalists. I employ too many of them. I don\'t sue journalists.', '"Never,Many,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I only buy a computer when it\'s two years old, after the glitches have been worked out."', '"Old,Two,Buy"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"There are jobs, particularly database-oriented ones, for which computers are necessary, but for everyday office life, I question whether they have brought the productivity that their enormous cost, up to ?10,000 per person, demands."', '"Life,Computers,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Computers are wasteful of paper and time. Once, we\'d get documents with a few errors. Now, people make hundreds of copies until each sheet is flawless and memos are duplicated endlessly. Managers get swamped with emails."', '"Time,Computers,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"The richer you are and the more financial advisers you employ, the less likelihood there is that you can ever discover what you are really worth."', '"Worth,More,Financial"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"The rich are not a contented tribe. The demands from others to share their wealth become so tiresome, so insistent, they often decide they must insulate themselves. Insulation eventually breeds a mild form of paranoia."', '"Wealth,Rich,Tribe"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"As with the onset of sudden celebrity, for the newly rich, the world often becomes a darker, narrower, less generous place; a paradox that elicits scant sympathy, but is nonetheless true."', '"Sympathy,World,True"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Very, very few entrepreneurs who accept a 51 percent partner in a new venture will get rich if they are also expected to run it. Control is mandatory."', '"Control,New,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I hear poets complaining: \'We face what our forebears did not face. We face TV. We face radio. We face this and that.\'', '"Face,Radio,Complaining"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Good ideas are like Nike sports shoes. They may facilitate success for an athlete who possesses them, but on their own they are nothing but an overpriced pair of sneakers. Sports shoes don\'t win races. Athletes do."', '"Success,Good,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'America is not the center of the universe.', '"Universe,America,Center"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"In the end, the railroads made America and nanotech will make the 21st century, and that is the end of the story. The beginning of the story and the end of the story."', '"America,Beginning,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"America, ladies and gentlemen, has done more for me financially than Britain ever has, or ever could have done."', '"Me,America,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"When you\'re writing, you\'re in a totally different zone... I can start a difficult poem and look up at the clock and see to my astonishment that three hours have passed."', '"Look,Difficult,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I\'ve been busy for years, buying land, often under pseudonyms, and planting trees on it. All the money is going into it when I die - and in the end I\'d like to think that it will be 20 to 30,000 acres."', '"Money,Busy,Die"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Poetry is one of the oldest of all art forms, and one of its powers for shamans and tribal leaders was the mnemonic."', '"Art,Poetry,Tribal"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"The planet doesn\'t require saving, and actually hasn\'t asked Greenpeace to save it."', '"Save,Planet,Greenpeace"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The climate has been changing since there was a climate.', '"Climate,Been,Since"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I have one talent, and that\'s figuring out what people want about two minutes before they know it themselves."', '"Talent,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"Unless you are completely retired, earning money is the best form of wealth preservation."', '"Best,Money,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Everything I publish is for my readers.', '"Everything,Publish,Readers"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"You cannot properly bring up children when you are 69 or 70 and they are 12 and at the height of their madness. You can physically do it, but I don\'t think it\'s morally justified."', '"Children,Madness,Height"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'People really do not have time to read all the newspapers in the world and all the sites that we now commonly use on the web. There is no possibility of keeping up.', '"Time,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'I\'ve always noted with some awe the reading habits of the Australian public. Australians read more newspapers and magazines per head of population than almost any other country in the world.', '"World,Country,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'The problem with rich lists is... it is impossible to know what someone is worth until they have died and you have sold it.', '"Impossible,Rich,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', '"I should have liked to get married, but over many decades I have lived essentially alone. I go to sleep when I\'m tired, get up when I wake up, have my food prepared when I\'m hungry. I can\'t bear the thought that I\'d have to coincide, make an effort."', '"Alone,Food,Tired"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'You can actually be bored stiff while you\'re dying.', '"Bored,Dying,While"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'False praise is worse than no praise.', '"Praise,Worse,False"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd18', 'Posthumous reputations have little to do with real lives.', '"Real,Little,Lives"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd19', 'I aspire only to silence.', '"Silence,Aspire,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd19', '"If Monsieur X spent an eternity studying treatises on optics, he would never paint \'La Grande Jatte.\'"', '"Never,Paint,Eternity"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'It is a wise man who said that there is no greater inequality than the equal treatment of unequals.', '"Wise,Man,Wise Man"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"Wisdom too often never comes, and so one ought not to reject it merely because it comes late."', '"Wisdom,Late,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"The real rulers in Washington are invisible, and exercise power from behind the scenes."', '"Power,Exercise,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"Gratitude is one of the least articulate of the emotions, especially when it is deep."', '"Emotions,Gratitude,Deep"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"Litigation is the pursuit of practical ends, not a game of chess."', '"Game,Chess,Litigation"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'Freedom of the press is not an end in itself but a means to the end of achieving a free society.', '"Freedom,Society,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'Old age and sickness bring out the essential characteristics of a man.', '"Age,Man,Old Age"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'It is a fair summary of history to say that the safeguards of liberty have been forged in controversies involving not very nice people.', '"History,People,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"To some lawyers, all facts are created equal."', '"Legal,Facts,Lawyers"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'The history of liberty has largely been the history of the observance of procedural safeguards.', '"History,Liberty,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'The ultimate touchstone of constitutionality is the Constitution itself and not what we have said about it.', '"Constitution,Said,Ultimate"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'I don\'t like a man to be too efficient. He\'s likely to be not human enough.', '"Man,Enough,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"All our work, our whole life is a matter of semantics, because words are the tools with which we work, the material out of which laws are made, out of which the Constitution was written. Everything depends on our understanding of them."', '"Life,Work,Life Is A"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"I came into the world a Jew, and although I did not live my life entirely as a Jew, I think it is fitting that I should leave as a Jew. I don\'t want to turn my back on a great and noble heritage."', '"Life,Great,World"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"As a member of this court I am not justified in writing my private notions of policy into the Constitution, no matter how deeply I may cherish them or how mischievous I may deem their disregard."', '"I Am,Matter,Cherish"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'It must take account of what it decrees for today in order that today may not paralyze tomorrow.', '"Today,Tomorrow,Order"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', '"It is anomalous to hold that in order to convict a man the police cannot extract by force what is in his mind, but can extract what is in his stomach."', '"Man,Police,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'The mode by which the inevitable is reached is effort.', '"Effort,Inevitable,Mode"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'Judicial judgment must take deep account of the day before yesterday in order that yesterday may not paralyze today.', '"Today,Day,Yesterday"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'There can be no security where there is fear.', '"Fear,Security,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'It simply is not true that war never settles anything.', '"War,True,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'Anybody can decide a question if only a single principle is in controversy.', '"Decide,Only,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'Answers are not obtained by putting the wrong question and thereby begging the real one.', '"Real,Wrong,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'We forget that the most successful statesmen have been professionals. Lincoln was a professional politician.', '"Politician,Professional,Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1a', 'The mark of a truly civilized man is confidence in the strength and security derived from the inquiring mind.', '"Strength,Man,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', 'I don\'t want to be just an average guy. I want to do whatever possible to win a lot of games. I\'m a competitor.', '"Win,Possible,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', '"When you work somewhere and you feel comfortable, you don\'t want to leave. You want to stay there forever."', '"Work,Feel,Forever"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', '"I\'m going to say this - to the people in Seattle, to all the people in Seattle that trust me, that believe in me - I\'m going to say this: I\'m not going to disappoint anybody."', '"Trust,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', 'I can\'t say anything I don\'t love about Seattle.', '"Love,Anything,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', '"Every year, you have to keep adjusting. I\'m 28; I\'m not 19 anymore. You have to work harder now."', '"Work,Year,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1b', '"In \'05, \'06, \'07 and \'08, I wasn\'t throwing any changeups at all. Maybe two or three per game. In \'09, I started playing with the grip, started throwing it in the bullpen and playing catch. It came out really good."', '"Good,Game,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1c', '"Everyone knows what a curve is, until he has studied enough mathematics to become confused through the countless number of possible exceptions."', '"Mathematics,Confused,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1c', '"The greatest mathematicians, as Archimedes, Newton, and Gauss, always united theory and applications in equal measure."', '"Always,Measure,Equal"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1c', '"Thus, in a sense, mathematics has been most advanced by those who distinguished themselves by intuition rather than by rigorous proofs."', '"Mathematics,Intuition,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1c', 'The developing science departs at the same time more and more from its original scope and purpose and threatens to sacrifice its earlier unity and split into diverse branches.', '"Science,Time,Sacrifice"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1d', 'The essence of the beautiful is unity in variety.', '"Beautiful,Unity,Essence"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1d', '"Though everything else may appear shallow and repulsive, even the smallest task in music is so absorbing, and carries us so far away from town, country, earth, and all worldly things, that it is truly a blessed gift of God."', '"God,Music,Gift"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1d', '"Ever since I began to compose, I have remained true to my starting principle: not to write a page because no matter what public, or what pretty girl wanted it to be thus or thus; but to write solely as I myself thought best, and as it gave me pleasure."', '"Best,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1d', '"People often complain that music is too ambiguous, that what they should think when they hear it is so unclear, whereas everyone understands words. With me, it is exactly the opposite, and not only with regard to an entire speech but also with individual words."', '"Music,Me,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1d', '"These seem to me so ambiguous, so vague, so easily misunderstood in comparison to genuine music, which fills the soul with a thousand things better than words."', '"Music,Me,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', '"At its core, banking is not simply about profit, but about personal relationships."', '"Banking,Profit,Personal"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', '"In the 1970s, New York City avoided bankruptcy because wise political leaders like Gov. Hugh L. Carey believed both in strong labor unions and robust banks and companies."', '"Wise,Political,City"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', 'I am a capitalist and I believe in making a profit.', '"Believe,I Am,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', 'Investment banking is not a business; it is a personal service where bankers work hand in hand with their clients. And it is a service that must not simply be about making bigger and bigger deals that reap rewards for only a small group of executives.', '"Work,Business,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', '"The early years of my life were very, very traumatic. It was scary, because any child knew that death was sort of lurking around Europe as far as Jews were concerned."', '"Life,Death,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', '"Throughout U.S. history, competent public investments have been an essential complement to private investments - from the Louisiana Purchase, to land-grant colleges, to the Interstate Highway System, to the Internet."', '"History,Internet,System"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd1e', '"The whole market mechanism and its evolution is something that, I\'m kind of of the Buffett School. You know, if I see a derivative, I run the other way."', '"Way,School,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', '"If someone had protected the HTML language for making Web pages, then we wouldn\'t have the World Wide Web."', '"World,Language,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', 'The ideal way to study the property of different types of neurons is to control individual types of cells independently and see what happens when you alter one type of cell. Optogenetics helps to realize this goal.', '"Way,Control,See"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', 'There may be an evolutionary advantage for schizophrenia genes during famine.', '"Genes,May,Schizophrenia"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', '"Brain cells are normally not sensitive to light. So by introducing light-sensitive proteins into specific types of neurons, we can now selectively control that specific type of neuron by shining light in the brain."', '"Brain,Light,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', '"Studies by many labs have already started to identify specific circuits of neurons involved in normal cognitive function like memory and learning, as well as disease processes such as Parkinson\'s disease, depression, and autism."', '"Learning,Memory,Depression"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd21', 'There are still many challenges and questions that need to be addressed before optogenetics can be applied in humans for therapeutic uses.', '"Challenges,Questions,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd22', 'A human society obeys the dictates of reason and is guided and governed by a respect for justice.', '"Respect,Society,Justice"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd22', '"We must not forget that chemical warfare will sooner or later bring in its wake bacteriological warfare, pest propagation, typhus and other serious diseases."', '"Will,Serious,Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd22', '"For a long time, it was believed that war was waged by armies which could not be identified with the nation itself. Professional soldiers took upon themselves the job of defending national interests, and it was understood that the war affected only them; the country itself went on living and working."', '"War,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd22', '"From the day war conquered the skies, nothing could check its progress."', '"War,Progress,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd23', '"It must inquire not merely about the circumstances of the time in general, but in particular about the writer\'s position with regard to these things, the interests and motives, the leading ideas of his literary activity."', '"Time,Ideas,Circumstances"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd23', 'It was my study of the two Corinthian letters that first caused me to concentrate my attention more directly on the relation of the apostle Paul to the older apostles.', '"Me,Attention,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd23', '"The greater the conceptual significance of a literary product, the more it should be assumed that it is based on an idea that determines the whole, and that the deeper consciousness of the time to which it belongs is reflected in it."', '"Time,Product,Consciousness"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd23', '"Without philosophy, history is always for me dead and dumb."', '"History,Me,Dumb"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Everyone, left to his own devices, forms an idea about what goes on in language which is very far from the truth."', '"Truth,Language,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', 'A linguistic system is a series of differences of sound combined with a series of differences of ideas.', '"Differences,Ideas,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Nearly all institutions, it might be said, are based on signs, but these signs do not directly evoke things."', '"Institutions,Signs,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"It is only since linguistics has become more aware of its object of study, i.e. perceives the whole extent of it, that it is evident that this science can make a contribution to a range of studies that will be of interest to almost anyone."', '"Science,Will,More"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"In general, the philological movement opened up countless sources relevant to linguistic issues, treating them in quite a different spirit from traditional grammar; for instance, the study of inscriptions and their language. But not yet in the spirit of linguistics."', '"Spirit,Language,Grammar"', '2023-05-29 11:41:00', '2023-05-29 11:41:00'),
	('391367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"It is one of the aims of linguistics to define itself, to recognise what belongs within its domain. In those cases where it relies upon psychology, it will do so indirectly, remaining independent."', '"Will,Independent,Define"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"In fact, from then on scholars engaged in a kind of game of comparing different Indo-European languages with one another, and eventually they could not fail to wonder what exactly these connections showed, and how they should be interpreted in concrete terms."', '"Game,Wonder,Connections"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', 'A language presupposes that all the individual users possess the organs.', '"Language,Individual,Organs"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Any psychology of sign systems will be part of social psychology - that is to say, will be exclusively social; it will involve the same psychology as is applicable in the case of languages."', '"Will,Social,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Henceforth, language studies were no longer directed merely towards correcting grammar."', '"Language,Grammar,Longer"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"It is useful to the historian, among others, to be able to see the commonest forms of different phenomena, whether phonetic, morphological or other, and how language lives, carries on and changes over time."', '"Time,See,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Linguistics will have to recognise laws operating universally in language, and in a strictly rational manner, separating general phenomena from those restricted to one branch of languages or another."', '"Will,Language,Rational"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Outside speech, the association that is made in the memory between words having something in common creates different groups, series, families, within which very diverse relations obtain but belonging to a single category: these are associative relations."', '"Words,Memory,Belonging"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"The business, task or object of the scientific study of languages will if possible be 1) to trace the history of all known languages. Naturally this is possible only to a very limited extent and for very few languages."', '"History,Business,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"The critical principle demanded an examination, for instance, of the contribution of different periods, thus to some extent embarking on historical linguistics."', '"Historical,Contribution,Principle"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"The first of these phases is that of grammar, invented by the Greeks and carried on unchanged by the French. It never had any philosophical view of a language as such."', '"View,Language,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"The very special place that a language occupies among institutions is undeniable, but there is much more to be said-, a comparison would tend rather to bring out the differences."', '"Differences,Place,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Whitney wanted to eradicate the idea that in the case of a language we are dealing with a natural faculty; in fact, social institutions stand opposed to natural institutions."', '"Stand,Language,Institutions"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2b', '"Within speech, words are subject to a kind of relation that is independent of the first and based on their linkage: these are syntagmatic relations, of which I have spoken."', '"Communication,Words,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'The most powerful weapon on earth is the human soul on fire.', '"Love,Fire,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', '"My center is giving way, my right is in retreat; situation excellent. I shall attack."', '"Way,Situation,Attack"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', '"Airplanes are interesting toys, but of no military value."', '"Value,Toys,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'The will to conquer is the first condition of victory.', '"Victory,Conquer,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', '"It takes 15,000 casualties to train a major general."', '"Train,General,Takes"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'In whatever position you find yourself determine first your objective.', '"Yourself,Find,Position"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'The power to command has never meant the power to remain mysterious.', '"Power,Never,Mysterious"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'A battle won is a battle which we will not acknowledge to be lost.', '"Battle,Lost,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd24', 'No study is possible on the battlefield.', '"Possible,Battlefield,Study"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', 'Labor is the source of all wealth and all culture.', '"Culture,Wealth,Labor"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', 'The constitutional questions are in the first instance not questions of right but questions of might.', '"Questions,Right,First"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"But you will understand by yourselves that the matter applies equally well to the organization of the officials of justice, of administrative officials, etc; these are likewise organized instruments of power in certain societies."', '"Power,Justice,Organization"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"Whoever lives in Berlin note, and doesn\'t die of Liberalism, will never die of vexation!"', '"Die,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"Useful as a war against France, undertaken by the Government against the will of the people would be for our revolutionary development, just so dangerous must be the effect upon our democratic development of a war supported by blind popular enthusiasm."', '"War,Government,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"Then this will only prove again and again, that Monarchy in Germany is he longer capable of a national act."', '"Will,Prove,Act"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"Only to he avoid misunderstandings, I must say that even last year, when I wrote my pamphlet, I heartily wished that Prussia should declare war against Napoleon."', '"War,Avoid,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', 'Only in a popular war against France... do I see a misfortune.', '"War,See,I See"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"From that moment on, the newspaper became a highly lucrative investment for those with a talent for making money or for publishers wanting to gain a fortune."', '"Money,Moment,Talent"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd25', '"But I felt all the more bound to make this proposal, because it at once turns to a reproach."', '"More,Because,Once"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"Once a champion, always a champion."', '"Champion,Always,Once"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"Leadership is the other side of the coin of loneliness, and he who is a leader must always act alone. And acting alone, accept everything alone."', '"Alone,Leadership,Loneliness"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'There are many things we do not want about the world. Let us not just mourn them. Let us change them.', '"Change,World,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Nobody is impervious to misfortune.', '"Nobody,Misfortune,Impervious"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Freedom is not just declared; it is exercised.', '"Freedom,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'I have Chinese blood in me... I am not ashamed to admit that perhaps the great leaders of our country all have Chinese blood.', '"Great,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"My countrymen: we have reached a turning point in our history. The choice is yours. Shall we venture into this brave new world, bright with possibilities, or retreat to the safety of our familiar but sterile past? I am for crossing the frontier."', '"History,World,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"Whatever be the challenges, whatever be the obstacles before us, I say to you as I say to everybody else that we will overcome."', '"Challenges,Obstacles,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I will fight to the last breath, even though my family cowers in terror in the palace."', '"Family,Fight,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'I often wonder what I will be remembered in history for. Scholar? Military hero? Builder?', '"History,Hero,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'I am not afraid to go to jail.', '"I Am,Go,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I\'ll take my destiny, whatever that may be, but I\'m going to fight for my dignity and my honor."', '"Fight,Destiny,Honor"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Filipino talents and skills are becoming ubiquitous in many parts of the world. Returning Filipino workers have helped improve our skills and technological standards.', '"World,Filipino,Returning"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"So long as I\'m president, communism will not thrive here."', '"Long,Will,Communism"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"These statements about torture, about alleged misuse of power and things like that, insulted the Filipinos more than their leader because it was made to appear as if Filipinos would tolerate a leader who would torture his own people, who would utilize his executive prerogatives for abuses."', '"Power,People,Torture"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I can feel it in my bones that no matter what we do, even if we do not do anything, the revolutionary government of Madame Cory Aquino will collapse."', '"Government,Feel,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'The permissiveness of society must be balanced with authoritativeness.', '"Society,Must,Balanced"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"History should not be left to the historians. Rather, be like Churchill. Make history, and then write it."', '"History,Like,Rather"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"To preserve our sovereign integrity, we must prove to them nobody need tell us how to hold a clean and democratic election."', '"Integrity,Election,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"America must realize, there are conditions she must accept in Asia. The first is a diversity of Asian cultures, governments, economic and political systems; the second, that to run against the tide of Asian nationalism is worse than impractical - it is also highly dangerous."', '"Political,Diversity,America"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'The U.S. State Department has a consistent record of error in the assessment of Asian situations and judging Red Chinese intentions.', '"Red,Assessment,Judging"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I was deposed by a coup d\'etat, by friends that I trusted and aided by the American Government."', '"Government,American,Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Little boys have amazing minds.', '"Amazing,Minds,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"The challenge to Asia is to discard the dry, meatless bone of mysticism and fatalism."', '"Challenge,Bone,Dry"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"Authority has to exist before it can be limited, and it is authority that is in scarce supply in those modernizing countries where government is at the mercy of alienated intellectuals, rambunctious colonels, and rioting students."', '"Government,Mercy,Authority"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"The one indisputable reality of dictatorship is that dissent, insult, and malevolent language do not go unpunished if it is allowed at all."', '"Reality,Dictatorship,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"Filipinos are not worse than any other colonized people except that our colonization was a little longer, and the independence movement was always dictated in political terms, never in social ones. We borrowed terms, but we didn\'t understand them."', '"Independence,Political,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'My life has been devoted to the upliftment of the Filipino by reestablishing his identity and dignity.', '"Life,My Life,Identity"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'I can understand the Cultural Revolution of Mao Tse-tung.', '"I Can,Revolution,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'The challenge to America is to extend to Asia the defensive shield of American power in forms consonant with Asian freedom and self-respect.', '"Freedom,Power,America"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"For us, overseas employment addresses two major problems: unemployment and the balance of payments position."', '"Balance,Problems,Position"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'What we ask of the developed countries is to let the Third World find a third way.', '"World,Way,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"The primary problem in many modernizing societies is not liberty but the creation of a legitimate public order. Men may, of course, have order without liberty, but they cannot have liberty without order."', '"Men,Liberty,Creation"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I do not care how brave a president is; I do not care how many medals he may wear. I do not care how well trained his guards may be. If he violates the will of the people, he shall be eliminated."', '"Brave,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"We do not postpone the participation of the lower classes of our people in the profits of economic enterprise, and in other countries, they do postpone it. In the long run, I think our policy is better, and we stand by it."', '"Long,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I have been called brave in my time, but brave as I may have been against foreign invaders, I have no heart to shed Filipino blood."', '"Time,Heart,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"To write our constitution is for the past, the present, and the future to come together all at once in one single motion, in one single heave, one single cry. For we correct the errors of the past and chart a new course for the future, based on the experience of the present."', '"Future,Experience,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"I am ashamed to run against a lady. It\'s demeaning, very degrading. I have always refused to argue with a lady."', '"I Am,Lady,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'President Reagan has no enemies in the Phillipines.', '"Enemies,President,Reagan"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'There is a standard joke in the family. Probably we should go into selling second-hand shoes.', '"Family,Shoes,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"We dare not supress thoughts, but when they are expressed through violence, like the idea that power comes from the barrel of a gun, they must be dealt with and met accordingly."', '"Power,Thoughts,Gun"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'How can I wage political battle against a widow who does not mean anyone any harm except only the president himself?', '"Political,Battle,Widow"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Let us not be so naive as to think that revolution is just a matter of social or economic discontent.', '"Matter,Revolution,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'Let us not be carried away by the undisguised agitations of leaders who virtually asked people to take the law into their own hands.', '"Law,People,Hands"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"In the Philippines, the host should always be willing to defer to the wishes of the guest."', '"Always,Wishes,Host"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"If it were true that special favors were given to some of these people because they are my cronies, then they should still be here, and they should be wealthy. But who are these cronies? If there be any cronies in government, point them out, and we will investigate."', '"Government,True,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'It is not true that I dictate what should be done. There is a dialogue.', '"True,Done,Dialogue"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', '"My friends in the opposition have forgotten that the constitution of the Philippines was amended in 1973 with their participation. The constitution mandates the administration, including the Batasan, or legislature, to convert slowly into a semiparliamentary form of government. The president in such a situation can issue decrees and edicts."', '"Government,Situation,Constitution"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'We have no quarrel with a policy that seeks to support human rights.', '"Support,Human Rights,Policy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd26', 'I would like to see whether my supposed successors can really operate the government without causing a crisis.', '"Government,See,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"Defenders of the status quo will argue that this system has served us well over the centuries, that our parliamentary traditions have combined stability and flexibility and that we should not cast away in a minute what has taken generations to build."', '"Will,Build,Stability"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'One of the unsung freedoms that go with a free press is the freedom not to read it.', '"Freedom,Free,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"For all its terrible faults, in one sense America is still the last, best hope of mankind, because it spells out so vividly the kind of happiness that most people actually want, regardless of what they are told they ought to want."', '"Happiness,Best,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"A majority in all parties do, I think, want to see local government recover its old vigour and independence."', '"Independence,Government,See"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'What the world needs now is more Americans. The U.S. is the first nation on earth deliberately dedicated to letting people choose what they want and giving them a chance to get it.', '"Chance,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"Something is happening to Britain and the British. Or has happened. We are said to be passing through a transition, or a turning point, or a transformation; nobody is quite sure which."', '"Transformation,Nobody,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"For the first half of this century, High Court judges have been cautious to the point of timidity in expressing any criticism of governmental action; the independence of the judiciary has been of a decidedly subordinate character."', '"Independence,Character,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"According to Richard Clarke, the former White House counterterrorism chief, Bush was so obsessed with Iraq that he failed to take action against Osama Bin Laden despite repeated warnings from his intelligence experts."', '"Intelligence,Action,White"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"All the research shows that being married, with all its ups and downs, is by far the most effective way of making young men law-abiding and giving them a sense of purpose and self-worth."', '"Men,Ups And Downs,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'America slept because most Americans preferred it that way.', '"America,Way,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'I think it\'s a pity that in many people\'s minds constitutional reform and PR have come to mean much the same thing.', '"People,Mean,Same Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"In real terms, there is a greater disparity of earnings between the very rich and the very poor."', '"Rich,Real,Poor"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'It\'s true that I\'m taking a break from writing a regular column to do other things but it\'s got nothing to do with what dear Simon has or has not written.', '"True,Nothing,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"No constitution is or can be perfectly symmetrical, what it can and must be is generally accepted as both fair and usable."', '"Constitution,Fair,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"Of course great politicians are always liable to be wrong about something, and the more people tell them they are wrong, the more stubbornly they defend their error."', '"Great,People,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"Sexual relations, of course, have existed, exist, and will exist. However, this is in no way connected with the indispensability of the existence of the family."', '"Family,Way,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'The president is being denounced for not taking the kind of pre-emptive action in Afghanistan that he has been so passionately denounced for taking in Iraq. Damned if he does and damned if he doesn\'t.', '"Action,He,Afghanistan"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'We are also further than ever from equality of opportunity.', '"Equality,Opportunity,Further"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', '"We criticize, copy, patronize, idolize and insult but we never doubt that the U.S. has a unique position in the history of human hopes."', '"History,Unique,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd27', 'We want a system that will improve consistency and steadiness in the quality of government.', '"Government,Consistency,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd28', '"If you fire people, you fire customers."', '"Business,Fire,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd28', '"In my career quite a few people have tried to force me out, but so far no one has succeeded."', '"Me,People,Far"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd28', 'During my career several people have tried to push me out the door... Nobody has succeeded yet.', '"Me,Door,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', '"I couldn\'t find the sports car of my dreams, so I built it myself."', '"Dreams,Car,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', '"If one does not fail at times, then one has not challenged himself."', '"Himself,Then,Fail"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', '"Design must be functional, and functionality must be translated into visual aesthetics without any reliance on gimmicks that have to be explained."', '"Design,Visual,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', 'A formally harmonious product needs no decoration; it should be elevated through pure form.', '"Product,Pure,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', 'Good design should be honest.', '"Good,Design,Honest"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd29', '"I came into the world at the same time as the auto, if you will."', '"Time,World,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2d', 'And the blood of brave men was shed like unto the shedding of rain from a black cloud.', '"Men,Rain,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2d', 'How shall a man escape from that which is written; How shall he flee from his destiny?', '"Man,Destiny,Escape"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2d', '"Helmet was joined to helmet, and spear to spear, and jewels, baggage, and elephants without number went with them, and you would have said it was a host that none could understand."', '"Understand,Helmet,Said"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2d', '"And now may the blessing of God rest upon all men. I have told unto them the Epic of Kings, and the Epic of Kings is come to a close, and the tale of their deeds is ended."', '"God,Men,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2d', '"Now when the two armies met, many and fierce were the combats waged between them, and blows were given and received, and swords flashed and showers of arrows descended on all sides."', '"Fierce,Two,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"For me, it\'s not about price. It\'s about necessity, quality, and usefulness. Like, I have my Wet N Wild 666 lip liner. It\'s 99 cents and always has been. I started using it when I was in high school, and it\'s great."', '"Great,Me,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I have always loved fashion because it\'s a great way to express your mood. And I\'m definitely a shoe lover. The right pair of shoes can change the feel of an outfit, and even change how a woman feels about herself. A woman can wear confidence on her feet with a high stiletto, or slip into weekend comfort with a soft ballet flat."', '"Change,Great,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"You know, I\'m a curvy woman and I just want to be comfortable with that."', '"Woman,Curvy,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"For me, I\'m not a jealous person. That\'s just not my thing. You have to have trust in your relationship."', '"Trust,Relationship,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I had so much fun developing and launching my first fragrance with Avon, so for my second fragrance, I really wanted to add a little more edge. Outspoken Intense is a provocative blend of sexy confidence and daring femininity that captures the thrill and excitement of being centre stage."', '"Sexy,Confidence,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Luckily I don\'t have to buy shoes anymore, because I design them! I\'m off tour, so I can dive in and create the shoes that I want for my line. But okay, I did buy a pair of vintage combat boots because they were so beaten up - I had to have them."', '"Design,Vintage,Shoes"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I finally found the product that helps mend my damaged hair and prevent breakage. Avon\'s Advance Techniques Damage Repair 3D Rescue Leave-In Treatment makes it look and feel healthier.', '"Look,Hair,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I have my team. Like if you see everyone around me - I have my hair and makeup girl, my assistant. They\'re very calm, they\'re all about positive energy. There\'re no drama queens. Everyone wants everyone else to have a positive experience. There are no agendas. I think it creates a healthy environment and there are no boundaries to cross."', '"Positive,Experience,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'m glad that our music motivates people to exercise. If I had to pick just one song to run to, it would be \'Violet\' by Hole. It makes me want to run."', '"Music,Me,Exercise"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'Wearing nice lingerie makes me feel really glamorous. I love to splurge on that.', '"Love,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'Dick Clark will be truly missed. We will carry on his legacy every New Year\'s Eve.', '"New Years,Legacy,New"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"In L.A., I get a meal delivery service called Diet Designs. I like a nice butter lettuce salad with some avocado, fresh grapefruit, shredded chicken breast and raw almond slices with a sesame vinaigrette dressing. I also love juicing and am kind of obsessed with it."', '"Love,Diet,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I\'m famous for splurging at fast-food places. I\'m currently obsessed with Taco Bell\'s bean and cheese burritos with extra green sauce and extra cheese. Gluttony!', '"Famous,Green,Bell"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'ve learned to suck in my stomach when photographers are around. I used to read gossip magazines all the time, but I stopped when I started being written about in them and read incredible lies about myself."', '"Time,Myself,Gossip"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'m a big online everything. But for me, shopping online started with music, obviously, then it went onto books, meditation CDs, and I just recently bought these electronic cigarettes. My husband is trying to quit smoking, so I went online and I bought those BluCigs cigarettes in every flavor for him."', '"Music,Me,Smoking"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I try to work out with my personal trainer for an hour, four times a week - we mainly concentrate on weights and running. If I\'m on the road I sometimes do DVD work-outs in my hotel room - P90X and Insanity are a couple of my favourites."', '"Work,Hotel,Road"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'You\'d be surprised how addicting high self-esteem is.', '"High,Self-Esteem,Surprised"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"The electro scene is all over the clubs now: groups like Duck Sauce, Empire of the Sun, even MGMT. But I get inspiration from everywhere. I\'ll go to the gym and put on old albums - Guns N\' Roses or old Jay-Z."', '"Duck,Sun,Roses"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"For me, healthy eating and exercising is something I work on constantly. I\'m not the most disciplined dieter. I try to eat a lot of fruit and vegetables but sometimes late at night I tend to have fast-food meals - and that\'s where I get myself into trouble! So I\'m not in the best shape I could be, but I\'m still healthy and comfy."', '"Work,Best,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I use the Clarisonic electronic skin cleansing system. It\'s great for removing excess oil and make-up and leaves my face feeling really smooth and clean. Then I apply Avon Anew Rejuvenate Day Revitalising Cream and Creme de la Mer Eye Concentrate. I think eye cream is so important - it keeps me looking young and prevents wrinkles.', '"Great,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'ve learned to be more accepting of myself. I\'m 37, not 18, and I\'ve got the lines to prove it. I try to remind myself that a girl can have it all, just not all at once."', '"Myself,Girl,Prove"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I don\'t miss being on the road right now because the thing is, I was on the road for eight years, so I love pizza, but pizza every day for eight years is a different thing."', '"Love,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'ve already got notebooks full of ideas for new music, so I\'m gonna kind of nurture that just like I do all of my ideas and perfect it until it\'s ready and then I\'ll just let it go."', '"Music,Perfect,New"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I needed to take a break from performing, and from the Peas, to be happy. I craved female time, and time with my husband to feed my soul. My life now is about being balanced. I\'m passionate about work and working out, seeing friends and family, and letting my hair down once in a while."', '"Life,Work,Family"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"There are so many different people that I\'ve emulated vocally. In the rock world - Sebastian Bach, Vince Neil, Freddie Mercury, Robert Plant. They all had amazing vocal talent."', '"Amazing,Plant,World"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"There is so much to do in my house, in every little corner. It\'s just like anybody, it\'s like one step at a time. I try to decorate one space and a pipe breaks or whatever - you know how it is."', '"Space,Time,Step"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'Guns are beautiful. But I don\'t like what they do.', '"Beautiful,Guns,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Once I have children, the kids come first. One thing at a time for me."', '"Time,Me,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I love black truffles. I love white truffles.', '"Love,Black,White"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Men scream and go crazy in the gym. I\'m a silent workout partner, but when my adrenaline gets up, I talk trash."', '"Men,Crazy,Partner"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"As far as female vocalists, I love Heart, Joan Jett, Courtney Love, Laura Branigan, Linda Ronstadt, Barbra Streisand - or going back to when I was a child, Aileen Quinn, the original Annie."', '"Love,Heart,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I know this sounds generic, but I\'m so happy to be home with my husband, my family, and my dog."', '"Family,Home,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I love Nelly. He\'s such a great performer. He\'s so hyper and so am I.', '"Love,Great,He"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I was a child actor. I was this spaz kid diagnosed with ADHD, and I worked all the time."', '"Time,Child,Actor"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I love diamond facials - they leave me glowing and refreshed.', '"Love,Me,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"There were periods of my life when a lot of people didn\'t believe in me. I still had faith in myself. I really had to ask myself life questions. Where do I see myself in five years? Create a ladder for yourself, and walk up the steps. Climb that ladder."', '"Life,Faith,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Right now I\'m reading every fashion magazine I can find. As a shoe designer, I feel it\'s my responsibility to learn as much as I can about the business, past and present."', '"Business,Responsibility,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'m trying to get a thicker skin. I like to be aware of people\'s perceptions of me, but when you put it as a priority, as a means to judging your worth, that\'s when it can be dangerous."', '"Me,Skin,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'ve been working straight since 2003, so I might just want to take an improv or theater class. That excites me. I can\'t wait to do different characters - not necessarily the leading chick who gets the guy, but the weird, freaky cousin."', '"Me,Wait,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I don\'t want to have a song like \'My Humps\' and it be sagging down, so I pay attention to that area. A lot."', '"Song,Attention,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I wasn\'t trying to be a role model with \'The Dutchess,\' but suddenly, seeing little girls in the audience with their moms made me think about what I do onstage a little bit more. I had to watch my mouth, because it can be filthy. It changed things for me."', '"Me,Role Model,Mouth"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Part of my affinity with urban music comes from being on \'Kids Incorporated,\' \'cos we used to sit around and listen to Chaka Khan and Prince, and I got influenced by all that. Then gangsta rap got started, and I was infatuated with that - maybe that\'s why I\'m fascinated by guns."', '"Music,Why,Sit"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"It\'s cool to express myself, but I\'ve had to learn that doing interviews isn\'t completely therapy - spilling everything about yourself isn\'t healthy all the time. But I\'ve been through things that have made me a stronger person, and if I can help some people, I will."', '"Cool,Time,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I love crying at romantic movies like \'The Notebook.\' I\'m always bawling.', '"Love,Romantic,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'m going through an evolution. I\'m completely cleaning out my closet. I\'m purging, because I saw that show \'Hoarders.\' I had a sweatshirt from sixth grade, and I\'m going, \'Why do I hold on to this?\'"', '"Why,Evolution,Cleaning"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"A lot of times on tour it\'s about, \'OK, where am I today? Wow, I\'m in Costa Rica. What is their famous dish?\' And it\'s about trying the food, and really experiencing it."', '"Food,Famous,Today"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"Grades were important in our house. I was reading by two. My mom would sit there and read with me, read with me, read with me. It was wonderful."', '"Mom,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I was in a group called Wild Orchid and it just wasn\'t working. I wasn\'t being myself. What I should have done was say. \'Girls, it\'s really time for me to go on my own. I need to fulfill this dream of mine to have a solo album.\' And I didn\'t know how to do that. I wanted to please them."', '"Time,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I\'m very close with my higher power. I have a very strong connection with it.', '"Power,Connection,Higher Power"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"So many songs are just a wink to the audience, but people take them seriously. \'My Humps?\' C\'mon!"', '"People,Seriously,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"What happens when you\'re a child professional is that you have to be, well, professional. You\'re taught not to have tantrums, to always people-please."', '"Always,Professional,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I call my therapist every other day. It\'s not a one-stop shop. You have to push away all that negativity in your head. Face it, name it, let it go."', '"Face,Day,Negativity"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', 'I have to wear two sports bras when I do my cardio. It takes a lot to hold these puppies up!', '"Sports,Cardio,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2e', '"I\'m very ambitious, but I also love myself - which means I try to take care of myself."', '"Love,Myself,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"Ambition drives you on, ability certainly helps, but the fickle finger of fate and luck are great things."', '"Great,Luck,Ambition"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"What worries me is that, because of the amount of media coverage of food, Britain seems to have become a foodie nation - but I\'m not sure it actually has. I\'m not sure there\'s been a huge change in the pantry at home or what we cook for supper."', '"Change,Home,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'I\'ve probably got lots of heroes. One is a chap called Charles Campbell - he is a wonderful chap. We cooked together in a nightclub in Notting Hill. He told me brilliant stories of food and life and generally put me on the right track.', '"Life,Food,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'Porridge and the urban lifestyle don\'t mix well.', '"Lifestyle,Well,Urban"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'I\'m a big believer that we get the politicians we deserve.', '"Politicians,Deserve,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'We live in a flat; my wife would be happy if we had a house with stairs. Or a little cottage in the country.', '"Wife,Country,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'I\'m like a kid in a sweet shop every day. It\'s slightly cringey how much fun I have.', '"Sweet,Fun,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"Do not let the word \'tripe\' deter you. Let its soothing charms win you over, and enjoy it as do those who always have!"', '"Win,Always,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"I had a holiday job in a kitchen, but I think we\'ll draw a polite veil over that. There was nothing joyous or creative about it. And none of this helped my studies."', '"Nothing,Kitchen,Holiday"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'My first proper kitchen was this funny little club that we set up in Mercer Street in Covent Garden. It got shut down. Then I worked at a club in Notting Hill.', '"Funny,Hill,Street"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"A pig\'s trotter is a fantastic thing. The first night of my honeymoon in Paris, my wife fell asleep in her steak tartare, so my trotter kept me company."', '"Wife,Night,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"Nose-to-tail eating is not a bloodlust, testosterone-fueled offal hunt. It\'s common sense, and it\'s all good stuff."', '"Good,Eating,Common Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"I feel good when I stir something with a spurtle, but I don\'t make porridge very much in London."', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"I think tripe is maligned. It\'s wonderful stuff, but everyone goes \'urgh.\' You have to wash and then cook it, very gently braise it, for eight hours. It uplifts you but steadies you at the same time."', '"Time,Everyone,Wonderful"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', 'I think Isambard Kingdom Brunel would be a good chap to have supper with. Anyone who builds a railway and then builds a steamship when he gets to Bristol and can\'t go any further must be a good chap.', '"Good,Go,Kingdom"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd2f', '"I cook British food, but it doesn\'t mean I\'m jingoistic about it. People can cook very good fusion food."', '"Good,Food,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd30', 'Mental attitude and concentration are the keys to pitching.', '"Attitude,Pitching,Concentration"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd30', 'All of the charities we\'re involved with have touched me in one way or another on a personal level. There are about eight or nine charities that I support.', '"Me,Support,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd30', 'I would love to see as many of the black players as possible in today\'s Major League Baseball make every effort to go to the Negro Leagues Museum and get a first-hand view of how it all started.', '"Love,Today,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', '"The restaurant business had a profound effect on my future and that of my two brothers. When we were able to stand on a stool to reach the sink, we washed dishes, and later, when we could see over the counter, we waited tables and managed the cash register."', '"Future,Business,Restaurant"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', '"The childhood poverty of both my parents and their minimal education did much to influence me and my two younger brothers in our education and career choices. One brother became a dentist and the other, a professor of anthropology with a Ph.D. degree."', '"Education,Childhood,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', '"My parents always encouraged us to get an education and establish a profession. However, my brothers and I grew up with considerable freedom, whether it was saving or spending our tips from the restaurant or our career choices."', '"Education,Freedom,Restaurant"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', '"Grade school, middle school and high school were relatively easy for me, and with little studying, I was an honor student every semester, graduating 5th in my high school class."', '"Me,Honor,School"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', 'I am not surprised that other gases may participate in cellular signaling and regulation. Our early work with nitric oxide was just the beginning. I\'m sure more will be discovered.', '"Work,I Am,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', 'Nitric oxide was known for destroying things.', '"Things,Known,Destroying"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', 'There are very few things in the body that nitric oxide doesn\'t regulate.', '"Body,Things,Few"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', 'I knew I wanted considerable education so that I wouldn\'t have to work as hard as my parents.', '"Education,Work,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd31', '"What does that suggest when a compound this simple plays such an important role? To me it suggests that nitric oxide is one of the most primitive elements of cellular signaling, that it goes way back into evolution."', '"Simple,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd32', '"History may be divided into three movements: what moves rapidly, what moves slowly and what appears not to move at all."', '"History,Three,Slowly"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd32', '"Everything must be recaptured and relocated in the general framework of history, so that despite the difficulties, the fundamental paradoxes and contradictions, we may respect the unity of history which is also the unity of life."', '"Life,Respect,History"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd33', 'Man needs colour to live; it\'s just as necessary an element as fire and water.', '"Fire,Water,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd33', 'This truth must be recognized as a dogma and assume the validity of an axiom in the general understanding of painting.', '"Truth,Painting,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd33', '"Enormous enlargements of an object or a fragment give it a personality it never had before, and in this way, it can become a vehicle of entirely new lyric and plastic power."', '"Power,Personality,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd33', 'The realistic value of a work is completely independent of its properties in terms of content.', '"Work,Value,Independent"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd33', '"What does that represent? There was never any question in plastic art, in poetry, in music, of representing anything. It is a matter of making something beautiful, moving, or dramatic - this is by no means the same thing."', '"Art,Music,Poetry"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The important thing is to win the title, and if we can do it with style and by entertaining, it\'s perfect."', '"Perfect,Style,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I believe my chances of making the World Cup squad will improve if I join City. My exposure would be better because Brazil is biased towards the Ukrainian league.', '"Believe,World,City"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Getting to the World Cup is a big dream for me.', '"Me,World,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"For me, the Premier League is the best tournament in the world. It\'s the hardest; you need to be 100 per cent to play every game."', '"Best,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In my country, we say that football is like a huge plate of food. Well, I want to eat everything because I want to win every trophy I can for City."', '"Food,Football,City"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I smile because I am a happy guy.', '"Smile,I Am,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Pep has made me understand the game more: not just how I play but also how the team has to play, because I am just a component."', '"Me,Game,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Most of the players can get injured, small ones and big ones. But when you get the small ones, you have to fight against them and play, play, play."', '"Fight,Big,Small"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In the end, we parted ways in good terms, and Shakhtar had a nice sending-off for me. I wish them well, and I am sure they feel the same."', '"Good,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Some of my friends wanted to do different things, but all I ever wanted to do was play outside with a ball."', '"Ball,Outside,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The first time was in Brazil, and the second time was when I was playing for Shakhtar against Inter in Milan. Fans were banned from the stadium on both occasions, and it is different. You have to keep your concentration on the pitch and try to win the game."', '"Time,Game,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"That is what it is like with Pep. At first, you don\'t understand. But then you grow up, you work, and now we understand the things he wants much better. It\'s not like the first season when it took him more time to make us understand his ideas. Some players didn\'t understand immediately what he wanted."', '"Work,Time,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I learned not to fight against the many bad things in football and try to always battle through injuries. That\'s one of the most important things I learned.', '"Football,Fight,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"For me, in football, everything is possible, and every game is a battle."', '"Football,Me,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I came to England because I thought it would help me to get back in the Brazilian national team.', '"Me,Back,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Occasionally, when I come off during a game, I get a little bit angry. But it\'s only because I want to play in every game and every minute to help my team-mates."', '"Angry,Game,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I just love to play and always want to be involved.', '"Love,Always,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"My body works best when I\'m playing all the time, so when I work more and I play more, I feel better."', '"Work,Best,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Willian is fantastic. It was good to be with him in Ukraine, where we won several titles together."', '"Good,Together,Titles"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"After I signed for Man City, the people back home in Brazil congratulated me for signing for one of the top teams."', '"Home,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"If I only wanted money and a comfortable life, I would have stayed in Ukraine."', '"Life,Money,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I was in Donetsk for eight years. I was happy there. I won six titles. I knew everyone, and I was a big part of the club."', '"Happy,Big,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Sometimes people mistake some things regarding that, thinking just one player would make up for the needs of an entire club."', '"Thinking,Mistake,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'City have been working throughout the years to mount competitive teams and pursue titles.', '"City,Pursue,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The City project is much more than about signing a single player with a strong name, that would eventually cost a lot more."', '"City,Name,Project"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"For me, it is the trophies that are important, not the goals."', '"Me,Goals,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'The titles are important forever; it doesn\'t matter when you win. They keep you motivated to win the Premier League and the Champions League.', '"Win,Important,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When you are a father, when you talk to your son or your daughter for the first time, they don\'t understand you. Of course, you have patience, and you keep talking to them, and eventually they do understand."', '"Patience,Time,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In my country, they used to call players who play in my position a defensive midfielder, but it is not defensive."', '"Country,Position,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The important thing to understand, from my point of view, is if the opponents break our lines and they are attacking our box, something has gone wrong, and it is me who has to fix it. But fouls in football are normal. You have to do it sometimes."', '"Football,View,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I am a nice guy.', '"I Am,Nice,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Sometimes you get players who are faster than you or who can trick you with some skill. Sometimes you make the foul.', '"Skill,Sometimes,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The English league itself is very strong physically, very demanding."', '"Strong,English,Itself"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Playing for Brazil is a huge pleasure. I think it\'s a huge pride.', '"Pride,Pleasure,Brazil"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When you\'re a child, you watch Brazil on TV and feel that desire to be a national team player, so when you get here, you make a dream come true, and it\'s a huge honour to me and to every player who wears the Brazil shirt."', '"Me,Shirt,True"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"The Selecao is always treated as favourites, so we\'re aware of our responsibility, and the goal is always to enter every competition to win, and the World Cup is no different."', '"World,Competition,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I\'ve always dreamed of playing in the World Cup and wearing the Selecao jersey, but I knew how difficult that was, what with me playing in Ukraine for Shakhtar."', '"Me,World,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I\'ve played a few times in stadiums where the fans have been banned, and it\'s just not the same."', '"Fans,Same,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Real Madrid are one of the main teams in Europe. They are a team which has won the Champions League the most times, a very good team, and known throughout the whole world as well."', '"Good,World,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Every player in every team speaks to each other in order to improve the quality on the pitch - that communication is necessary.', '"Communication,Quality,Order"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I like every competition I can play.', '"Competition,I Can,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When you win a title, you gain confidence, and the supporters love you because they want to win things as well."', '"Love,Confidence,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Wembley is special.', 'Special', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In the Premier League, the most important thing is not to give the team at the top of the table reasons to keep winning game after game."', '"Game,Winning,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Playing in the Premier League for City is like a dream.', '"City,Dream,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Playing for a huge club in a huge League makes me so happy.', '"Me,Happy,Club"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Whoever wants to be champions has to be able to attack and defend.', '"Attack,Able,Defend"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"If you play bad, you can win the games, but you have to play good and get the three points."', '"Good,Bad,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Would I have preferred not to play in a home World Cup for Brazil, a privilege that most people in this world can only dream of? Not a chance."', '"Home,Chance,World"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I have heard what has been said, but most of the time, I recover the ball without making a foul."', '"Time,Ball,Said"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In football, contact is normal, especially in England."', '"Football,Normal,Contact"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Pep and his staff work very hard, not just on the training pitch but also with the analysis of opponents, and now, of course, we understand more how he wants to play."', '"Work,Training,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"No matter how great a squad is, a competition like the Champions League is not easily won."', '"Great,Competition,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Shakhtar specifically are proud when traditional clubs from Europe come knocking, and I knew it would be quite hard to convince them to let me join City. Listen, I am absolutely thankful for the opportunity they gave me, but I also think I worked my socks off for that club, and it was time to look after my career."', '"Time,Thankful,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I watched Romario when I was young, and he was one of my idols."', '"Young,Idols,He"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'We all know the Premier League is a competitive league and that every game is competitive.', '"Game,Know,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Manaus has got nothing in relation to Brazilian football history.', '"History,Football,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"My father and uncles all encouraged me to play football: every present I ever got would be boots, kit, or a new ball, and that was just how I liked it."', '"Football,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I moved cities when I was 17, and I moved countries when I was 20. Every time, I put football at the forefront and, if you do that, you don\'t have such a hard time settling in."', '"Time,Football,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Since I was 13 years old, I made sure I was going to training every day."', '"Training,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'The Premier League is considered the best league in the world.', '"Best,World,Premier League"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"You think about past World Cups - in 2006, it was a fantastic Brazil team, but we did not do so well that year. In 2010, the same: it did not go far, either - only the quarter-finals. But in \'94 and 2002, Brazil did not play the best football but won the World Cup; they found a way to win."', '"Best,Football,World"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I listen to the Manchester news on local radio. It has helped me learn English. I have it on when I am driving to training in the morning.', '"Morning,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When I was young, I would drive so fast. Now I see it a different way."', '"Drive,Way,Fast"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Football doesn\'t depend just on your brain. It\'s not like on a computer. It depends on your body, too, and sometimes you are tired. Sometimes the opponent closes the space very well and marks you very well. Football depends on many things, not just on you."', '"Space,Football,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"We all know the Premier League is so tough and many, many things can happen - right until the last game of the season."', '"Game,Tough,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When you have this desire to win, to win, to win, I would not feel comfortable losing a title."', '"Feel,Win,Losing"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"It\'s good when you score goals because you are helping your team. For yourself as well, it\'s good, but the most important thing is the strength of the team."', '"Strength,Good,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"If you want to win the Premier League, you have to win away as well."', '"Win,Well,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I personally like Kolarov. He is one of the funniest players I have played with. Every day, he has something new, and he is a funny guy!"', '"Funny,Day,New"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I like to hear BBC Manchester about the news and to learn English and the Manchester accent.', '"News,Hear,Accent"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"One of the positive things about Pep is that he is so close with his staff - they support him in every situation, and we, as players, have huge contact with them."', '"Positive,Support,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"As a human, as a professional player, you have to improve every day, every training session, every game."', '"Game,Training,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'It\'s always difficult when you have had a game in midweek to get to a final.', '"Game,Difficult,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'We know the FA Cup is important for the team and fans.', '"Fans,Important,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"It is not a problem - you don\'t think about the climate, or the cold; we just think about winning the game."', '"Game,Winning,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Of course, when you lose any game, the feeling is so bad. But you have to be professional and have to be clever and overcome this situation and try to work on that and try to fix the problem and solve for the next game."', '"Work,Game,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"With Pep in charge, I feel sure we can win significant silverware and, importantly, we will try to do it playing attractive, attacking football."', '"Football,Feel,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I don\'t think City play a Brazilian style - it is more Spanish the way we play here.', '"City,Style,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'You need to be ready for all situations.', '"Ready,Need,Situations"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'To be able to battle is very important.', '"Battle,Important,Able"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'It is always tough to play against Norwich.', '"Tough,Always,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'The Premier League is always like that - you never know what can happen! Even at the top of the table and bottom of the table.', '"Never,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"I spent eight years in Ukraine, and I played against Kiev many times."', '"Against,Ukraine,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Having trust in your manager is the most important thing for a footballer.', '"Trust,Important,Footballer"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"It is impossible to do it for the whole game, but when you have the ball for most of the game and have players like Samir Nasri, David Silva, Yaya Toure, and Raheem Sterling, they keep the ball so well."', '"Impossible,Game,Ball"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Every player at a high level faces pressure and must respond, and I am ready for that, too."', '"I Am,Pressure,Ready"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I hope I will be able to repay City for what they have done for me.', '"Hope,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I know a lot about City.', '"City,Know,About"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"My first aim is to play well for my club, Manchester City. If I do, I am sure that will come to the attention of the national manager."', '"City,I Am,Aim"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"In Ukraine as well as in Brazil, Manchester City is now considered one of the best teams in the world, and after I signed, people back home in Brazil congratulated me for signing for one of the top teams in the world."', '"Best,Home,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"It is not easy to play two games, travel, and keep the same performance in 48 hours."', '"Travel,Performance,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"It is always good when you play away because the fans support their team, and it gives you more motivation to play well."', '"Good,Support,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'Champions League matches are not always played on good pitches.', '"Good,Always,Champions League"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"When you play on bad surfaces, you have to show your character and keep your concentration for the whole 90 minutes."', '"Character,Bad,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'There are a lot of people in England with good football knowledge.', '"Knowledge,Good,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"Pellegrini is always calm; if you have problems, he will try to resolve it."', '"Calm,Problems,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'I was so happy to finish my first season in England with two trophies.', '"Happy,Finish,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', 'The first season in a new country like England is very difficult.', '"Difficult,New,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd34', '"If someone was ever racist towards me, I would go wild."', '"Me,Wild,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I am very proud to be part of this team, and I know that winning with Ferrari will mean more than winning with another team."', '"I Am,Winning,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"Every day, every year, every new season is a reset from the last, and you are still hungry for success, to do things better and better."', '"Success,Day,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I have always been very calm on the outside. I\'m not too stressed now just because I\'m in formula one. For me, tomorrow will be another day whether I finish first or last. I have to do the maximum and I cannot ask any more from myself."', '"Myself,Tomorrow,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I am one of the best to have raced in F1. I am probably not fastest in qualifying, or the wet, but I am 9.5 in all areas. I try to benefit from that."', '"Best,I Am,F1"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"Creating a top team and being in a position to win the Tour de France will give me a nice feeling. But I know it is not easy to create a top team from zero. You need good riders, good staff, a lot of preparation and, most important, a lot of sponsors."', '"Good,Me,Preparation"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I always had that, even when I was a kid in a go-kart or when I was playing soccer or tennis: that need of winning. It was there all my life, and it\'s still there now."', '"Life,My Life,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I like to race, not to do laps alone."', '"Alone,Race,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I miss winning. I miss being on the podium.', '"Winning,Being,Miss"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I am a very competitive person in everything. Not only F1 but in everyday life.', '"Life,I Am,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"For me, it was not destiny to make it to where I am now - I thought for a long- time I would become a go-kart mechanic, or a job like this, not an F1 driver."', '"Time,Me,Destiny"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'In Spain there were no TV rights for Formula One.', '"Formula One,Rights,Formula"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I am very proud of what we have built in Spain, because it is not a traditional Formula 1 country. I think we have found passionate fans, and built up a strong culture for the sport - and things are improving every day, with more and more people getting interested."', '"Culture,I Am,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'The day that arrives the first victory or the first win for McLaren-Honda will be a massive achievement for all of us.', '"Achievement,Victory,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I would not be happy if I had many trophies at home and people think I don\'t deserve them.', '"Home,People,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"If you\'re in the best team in the world, you or your teammate have to win."', '"Best,World,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'For me it\'s a simple sport and a simple way to live these seven or eight years of maximum sport.', '"Simple,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I like America, and I think probably the American people like me."', '"Me,America,People"', '2023-05-29 11:42:00', '2023-05-29 11:42:00'),
	('391690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I don\'t want to just be a good driver: I want to be a complete driver and hopefully the best driver in the world.', '"Best,Good,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'To be one of the names being talked about is better than not. But it\'s only talking.', '"Better,Talking,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"It is true - maybe with five or seven points more, I could be five times world champion. But on the other hand, I could have zero world championships, and zero wins or zero podiums, because F1 is an extremely competitive environment. So I just take the positives, and I am happy with my achievements."', '"I Am Happy,World,Champion"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I look at myself as someone who has been very lucky - my job is also what I enjoy most in the world, and I can make my life doing it."', '"Life,Myself,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"When I take go-karts out with my friends, it\'s a disaster normally. But in the race car, I\'m calm because they pay me to do this, and I have to be professional."', '"Car,Me,Calm"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I feel extremely lucky and privileged to have my achievements.', '"Feel,Lucky,Privileged"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"You can play basketball and have a magic night and score 40 points with your team-mates and win the game. There are favourites for the World Cup, but you can\'t guarantee Germany, Spain, or Brazil will win, but here, everyone can guarantee that Mercedes or Ferrari will win the race, and this is very sad for the sport."', '"Sad,Night,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"Even if you have a difficult season, you still believe the following year will be better and a good one."', '"Good,Believe,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"When I joined F1, I was 19 years old, full of energy."', '"Energy,F1,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'Ferrari gives you a special feeling.', '"Special,Feeling,Ferrari"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'When I race in Australia or Korea or Japan I know it will be a big change for me because Ferrari fans are worldwide.', '"Change,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"When I race in Australia or Korea or Japan, I know it will be a big change for me because Ferrari fans are worldwide. It\'s very nice if you win, but it\'s not so good if you lose. All this is part of being a Ferrari driver."', '"Change,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"After five years in Ferrari, being second all the time, I think it was enough for me."', '"Time,Me,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"McLaren was a risky project because they were completely new, but we are one team - we win and we lose together."', '"Together,Lose,New"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"With Ferrari sometimes, you win or you lose depending on what the mood of the team in general, of the group in general."', '"Lose,Mood,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'The Triple Crown is an attractive target because it is so difficult to achieve.', '"Difficult,Crown,Attractive"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"If you challenge yourself and try to be the best in all areas, you have to be a complete driver."', '"Best,Yourself,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'My parents are very similar to me.', '"Me,Parents,Similar"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'It is difficult to take in how long you have been doing one thing when you compete at the highest level and always with the highest intensity.', '"Long,Difficult,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I\'m just hungry to win.', '"Win,Hungry,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'My idea is to win all the iconic motor sport races in the world.', '"World,Win,Motor"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', 'I want to live a normal life that I never had the opportunity to do for many years.', '"Life,Opportunity,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"In life, it\'s winning - when I go to the supermarket, and I go with a friend, I try to get through the door first. Things like that - everything in life is a competition for me."', '"Life,Me,Competition"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd35', '"I adapt my driving style more or less to anything, from go-kart to motorbike to wet, more downforce, less downforce, Pirelli, Bridgestone, Michelin, V8, V6, whatever."', '"Style,Anything,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Sketching is almost everything. It is the painter\'s identity, his style, his conviction, and then color is just a gift to the drawing."', '"Sketching,Gift,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'Art should be an oasis: a place or refuge from the hardness of life.', '"Life,Art,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"The circus allows one to be logical and unreal at the same time. In the circus, all is possible: there can be a man with two heads or a character with a green face."', '"Time,Green,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"My work is a self-portrait of my mind, a prism of my convictions."', '"Work,Mind,Convictions"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"There\'s nothing more superficial to do than to paint a beautiful woman. The most beautiful portraits in art were of ugly women. If you paint Brigitte Bardot, it\'s a disaster. Sunsets, you have to stay away from sunsets. You paint a sunset, you are in great danger."', '"Women,Art,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'An artist is attracted to certain kinds of form without knowing why. You adopt a position intuitively; only later do you attempt to rationalize or even justify it.', '"Why,Position,Knowing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Art is always an exaggeration in some sense; in color, in form, even in theme, etc... but it has always been this way. It is the same with the nature of some works by Giotto or Massacio, or the color of life as expressed by Van Gogh."', '"Life,Nature,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I was drawing a mandolin, and I made the sound hole very small, which made the mandolin look gigantic. I saw that making the details small made the form monumental. So in my figures, the eyes, the mouth are all small, and the exterior form is huge."', '"Eyes,Look,Drawing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I believe that it\'s better to have a conviction, believe strongly in something, and then the convictions create a style that reflects your mentality."', '"Believe,Style,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"An artist is born like a priest is born. If they are born an artist, I would tell them art is not a game: it is something very serious which completely requires everything you have to give."', '"Art,Game,Serious"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Nobody ever told me, \'Art is this.\' This was good luck in a way because I would have had to spend half of my life forgetting everything that I had been told, which is what happens with most students in schools of fine arts."', '"Life,Good,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I\'m the most Colombian of the Colombians, even though I\'ve lived 47 years outside of Colombia. I\'ve lived 13 years in New York, and I never did a painting about New York. I\'ve lived in France more than 30 years, and I\'ve never painted Paris."', '"Painting,New,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I love my country, and it hurts not to be able to see my country, as I did for so many years. I hope that I will one day be able to live in a peaceful Colombia."', '"Love,Hope,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'You paint what you know best; what you went through as a teenager and child. My world is the one I got to know in Medellin; I never paint anything else other than that.', '"Best,World,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"The circus is a global theme. It exists in all parts of the world - maybe not in Africa, but it exists in Asia in all parts. In Latin America, it\'s difficult to find a person who hasn\'t gone to the circus."', '"World,America,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"In a photo, you just do a click, but in art you have to put in so much energy. This concentration of energy and attention says something that other media cannot say."', '"Art,Energy,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'The only duty an artist has is in the quality of the art. There is no moral obligation to denounce. An artist confronted with a tremendous injustice sometimes feels inclined to say something. Denouncing the situation is the artist\'s choice.', '"Art,Quality,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I have the sensation of doing something good for people, more than being a trendy artist or a successful artist."', '"Good,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I often think about death, and it saddens me to leave this world and not be able to paint more. I love it so much."', '"Love,Death,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I had wanted to be a sculptor throughout life, but to do so, I had to stop painting."', '"Life,Painting,Stop"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I have seen Colonial churches since I was very small, Colonial painting and polychrome sculpture. And that was all I saw. There was not a single modern painting in any museum, not a Picasso, not a Braque, not a Chagall. The museums had Colombian painters from the eighteenth century and, of course, I saw Pre-Columbian art. That was my exposure."', '"Art,Painting,Small"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'I follow politics very closely. I read several newspapers every day.', '"Politics,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Art is important because when people start to forget, art reminds them what happened. Like \'Guernica.\' People would not remember the tragedy of Guernica today if it were not for that painting."', '"Art,Today,Painting"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"In the \'60s, I did many satirical portraits of dictators."', '"Did,Dictators,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"My popularity has to do with the divorce between modern art, where everything is obscure, and the viewer who often feels he needs a professor to tell them whether it\'s good or not. I believe a painting has to talk directly to the viewer, with composition, color and design, without a professor to explain it."', '"Good,Art,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"People say, \'What a discipline, painting so much.\' I say, \'No, I love it.\' Nothing amuses me as much as my work. To have discipline would be not to paint."', '"Love,Work,Discipline"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I had an uncle who took me to the ring in Medellin when I was 15 years old. In school, we had someone who taught us how to bullfight."', '"Me,School,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Before anything else, I started painting bulls and matadors. That was my initiation to paint."', '"Painting,Anything,Paint"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Bullfights have so much color. Not just the matador but also the bull, the arena, and the public. It\'s all very festive."', '"Bull,Color,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"Bullfights are a very cultural thing. I know many people think it\'s cruel, but so many things are cruel. Hunting, the electric chair, wars. These are all cruel things as well."', '"People,Chair,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'Expression without culture is flat. Many artists come out of art school and start doing things that don\'t last. They are audacious because of ignorance. They are irresponsible.', '"Art,Culture,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"All my life, my girlfriends are always skinny. Beauty in art has nothing to do with beauty in reality. Why do you like primitive art? Because there is beauty in the deformity. Sometimes paintings that people consider realistic are not at all. Raphael figures look realistic, but in real life, they were deformed."', '"Life,Beauty,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', '"I love art so much because of curiosity. At the start of a painting, I know 10 percent of what the painting will be, and then I have to improvise the whole thing."', '"Love,Art,Painting"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'The circus leaves a sweet memory.', '"Sweet,Memory,Circus"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd37', 'All the animals I\'ve painted always have a relationship with man. I have been told that part of the knowledge of the human anatomy comes from animals.', '"Knowledge,Relationship,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'Great work is done by people who are not afraid to be great.', '"Work,Fear,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'Hope is the raw material of losers.', '"Hope,Losers,Raw"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"When trust improves, the mood improves."', '"Trust,Mood,Improves"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"I made my own assessment of my life, and I began to live it. That was freedom."', '"Life,Freedom,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'Our best comes out when we have honest discussions.', '"Best,Our,Out"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'You have to be able to risk your identity for a bigger future than the present you are living.', '"Future,Identity,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"When I left prison, I had to figure out how to embrace my past."', '"Past,Prison,Embrace"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'You have one big mythology in your favor: Everyone believes that you Europeans are impeccable. But I know you are jerks.', '"Know,Big,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'Our worst comes out when we behave like robots or professionals.', '"Worst,Robots,Behave"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"I never told a victim story about my imprisonment. Instead, I told a transformation story - about how prison changed my outlook, about how I saw that communication, truth, and trust are at the heart of power."', '"Trust,Truth,Communication"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"That\'s why we\'re doing this, to defend our traditions a little. I don\'t have anything against it (Halloween), but it\'s not our tradition."', '"Doing,Why,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"I never blamed Pinochet, or my torturers, or external circumstances."', '"Never,Circumstances,External"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', 'A feel-good style can be a symptom of unawareness or lack of caring.', '"Style,Caring,Lack"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd38', '"But every company of the future is going to be in the business of exquisite care - which means quick turnaround time and convenience. To deliver exquisite care, you need an organization that coordinates well and listens well."', '"Future,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"For the conservatives, Lula is seen as someone who constantly seeks demarcation and even rupture. For the Left, however, Lula is always seen as someone who conciliates, as he acknowledges the role of owners in improving the conditions of workers."', '"Always,Someone,Seen"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'Brazil needs peace and not hate.', '"Peace,Hate,Brazil"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"If you want to be able to teach, then you need to listen - a lot."', '"Need,Want,Able"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"In the nineties, the PT had wrongly decided to attribute its electoral failures to its virtues."', '"Virtues,Had,Nineties"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'What seems not yet to have been sufficiently explored is the emancipating potential of the discursive form of psychoanalysis in politics as a counterpoint of marketing.', '"Politics,Potential,Marketing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Taken as a whole, the work of Marx, at the same times it shows the thesis of the growing pauperization of the non-propertied classes, relativizes it when contemplating the possibility that the class struggles result in distributive effects."', '"Work,Result,Thesis"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"I would say that I am an academic in politics. I have never abandoned my academic approach to observe reality, independently from the subject and its constant changes."', '"Politics,Reality,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Lula\'s foreign policy goal was to turn Brazil into a sub-imperial power, with a presence in Africa, Asia, and the Middle East. This strategy must be understood as a reaction to his concerns that the extractive sector would threaten Brazil\'s industrial tissue."', '"Power,Strategy,Brazil"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Lula\'s political culture translated into a government project that sought to include the poor in the budget with minimal efforts in terms of structural transformation. The inclusion of the poor would trigger the economy, creating a virtuous cycle of mass consumption market, increased tax collection, more investments, and more benefits."', '"Government,Political,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"My master\'s was in economics, and my Ph.D. was in philosophy, and I became a professor at USP. But after three years, I was invited to be secretary of finance for Sao Paulo mayor Marta Suplicy. They reached out to be because of my economics background."', '"Finance,Economics,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"My father - a Lebanese-origin small businessman - had a stroke in 1997 and couldn\'t work anymore. I paused my career and made sure he was taken care of by overseeing the sale of his businesses, but after that, I was able to dedicate myself to politics. It\'s what I had always wanted."', '"Politics,Work,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"A lot of people abroad know Lula\'s campaigns against poverty and hunger, but he had a tremendous legacy in education too. He invested 2 percent of GDP, more than other administration, putting the PT\'s education programs in motion."', '"Education,Legacy,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Lula aimed to both internationalize big Brazilian capital and improve the domestic market and the condition of the poorest in Brazil. In the gaze of a lot of people, this was a big contradiction, but for Lula, this was the most natural thing in the world, to think about these two things together."', '"Together,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'We combine fiscal responsibility with social responsibility.', '"Responsibility,Social Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Without public investment, without families spending, without cheap credit, the economy won\'t recover."', '"Investment,Credit,Cheap"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"Bolsonaro is a tropical Trump. They have a very common agenda, a very regressive agenda, when it comes to civil rights, social rights, and environmental rights."', '"Environmental,Social,Rights"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'Bolsonaro is adopting a regressive policy as regards rights but a neoliberal policy when it comes to economic policy.', '"Policy,Rights,Economic"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"To be consistent with this discourse of lifting up the military dictatorship in Brazil, the dictatorship that extended from 1964 to 1985, Bolsonaro, his whole life, has been uplifting not only the dictatorship itself but also the methods that the dictatorship used to stay in power, including torture."', '"Life,Power,Dictatorship"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"The objective of politics is always to build scenarios in which persons\' horizons can be expanded evermore. Any political action that is aimed at restricting individuals\' horizons is, as I see it, a regressive action in relation to the political values that I embrace."', '"Politics,Political,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'A president with a pen in their hand is a very powerful person.', '"Pen,Person,Powerful"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'Everyone knows that the Workers\' Party governments did much more good than bad for the country.', '"Good,Bad,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'The Workers Party rose to power when the Western Left began its descent.', '"Power,Rose,Workers"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'Lula is off the charts. You cannot reproduce Lula; and you will always have to count him in.', '"Will,Always,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'No one thinks of controlling inflation of a continental-sized country by holding back municipal tariffs. Macroeconomic stability cannot be achieved through microeconomic intervention.', '"Country,Back,Inflation"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'Brazil must resume and deepen Latin American integration.', '"American,Brazil,Resume"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"When I\'m out there on the streets, I enjoy meeting people and listening to their complaints and critiques. It\'s something that I take great pleasure in."', '"Great,People,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', '"I really believe in the power of social control coming from within the community itself. The community protecting itself, its children, its teenagers, you know? I think that\'s far more effective than a police presence."', '"Power,Community,Police"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd39', 'I\'m against using Petrobras to combat inflation.', '"Inflation,Against,Combat"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3a', 'It is better to look good than to feel good.', '"Good,Feel Good,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3a', 'You look marvelous!', '"Look,Marvelous,You"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', '"Look, there\'s no metaphysics on earth like chocolates."', '"Valentines Day,Look,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', 'All is worthwhile if the soul is not small.', '"Soul,Small,Worthwhile"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', '"Could it think, the heart would stop beating."', '"Heart,Stop,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', 'Wise is he who enjoys the show offered by the world.', '"Wise,World,He"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', '"To feel today what one felt yesterday isn\'t to feel - it\'s to remember today what was felt yesterday, to be today\'s living corpse of what yesterday was lived and lost."', '"Today,Lost,Yesterday"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', '"Success consists in being successful, not in having potential for success. Any wide piece of ground is the potential site of a palace, but there\'s no palace till it\'s built."', '"Success,Ground,Palace"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', 'No intelligent idea can gain general acceptance unless some stupidity is mixed in with it.', '"Stupidity,Acceptance,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', 'To choose ways of not acting was ever the concern and scruple of my life.', '"Life,My Life,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3b', '"At first, it\'s unfamiliar, then it strikes root."', '"First,Then,Root"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Football is a team sport and not an individual sport. We win as a team, and every individual is better if we are part of the team."', '"Football,Better,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'The things you cannot change you can\'t waste your time on.', '"Change,Time,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"It\'s not easy to come somewhere new and have to find your place. You might feel someone doesn\'t like you, or you might need to find new friends. It\'s not easy, and I don\'t like this kind of thing. It\'s not easy, so you want to protect the players who are alone."', '"Alone,New Friends,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"In your life, you go through a difficult situation or a very good situation, and you have different moods, but you learn things from your experiences."', '"Life,Good,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Steven Gerrard is the best player I have played with throughout my career; therefore, my ideal player would be very like him."', '"Best,Ideal,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'You have to prove yourself every day. You have to live for today.', '"Today,Yourself,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I can be very shy. I really like to stay at home with my people because I\'m really shy. My wife is as well; we\'re both really shy.', '"Home,Wife,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I want to thank my two English clubs: Liverpool for bringing me to the Premier League and Chelsea for the trophies I won.', '"Me,Two,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Liverpool gave me a second home. I was 24, I left my team, my town, and I went there. My memories there are just amazing. I have no words to thank them enough, and that\'s why I will always be a fan."', '"Home,Amazing,Memories"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"My son is a Liverpool fan, and he was already kicking a ball before he was one. He was born in the football city; he had no choice."', '"Football,City,Choice"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I am a big fan of the Gallagher brothers. At Liverpool, they came a few times; they are friends of Steven Gerrard. It was nice to meet them. When I was in Spain, I couldn\'t speak English, so I couldn\'t understand the lyrics. When I came to England, I started studying music and trying to understand what my favourite songs said."', '"Music,I Am,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I was not a Liverpool fan or a Chelsea fan in Madrid. I was an Atletico fan. I still am. Maybe they\'re the only badge I will kiss.', '"Kiss,Will,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Madrid is not as big as London, but it is true when you are coming from a big city like Madrid, nothing is going to surprise you, and I am very happy to move to a city like London. It is a big city, and you can do everything you want with the respect that the English people always have."', '"Respect,Surprise,City"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Fitness is important, but the most important thing is how you adapt and the way you feel physically. To adapt to a new position. To try to change your game."', '"Change,Fitness,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I don\'t want to imagine the time when I have to stop playing.', '"Time,Stop,Imagine"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I like to play. It doesn\'t matter if it\'s just me up front on my own or alongside another striker. I always want to play in the first XI.', '"Me,Always,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Big clubs in Europe always go through difficult spells where it appears as though there is no light at the end of the tunnel. But because they are big clubs, they always come back, and they do so with a vengeance."', '"Light,Difficult,End Of The Tunnel"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When I was a child, my dream was to play for Atletico."', '"Child,Dream,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'You have to win with the team and for the team.', '"Win,Team,You"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Chelsea gave me all the trophies I have as a football player. I saw my kids growing up in London.', '"Football,Me,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Winning the European Championship was a great thing for me, and I understood what it was to win a major trophy and what I had been missing."', '"Great,Me,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Nobody has ever gifted me anything.', '"Me,Nobody,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I was captain in Atletico at 19, playing in the same team as Demetrio Albertini, who won three Champions Leagues, and Sergi Barjuan from Barcelona, who had won everything, and they were 32, 33. I was a kid as captain, so I wasn\'t the real captain, just a kid learning from them."', '"Learning,Captain,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I didn\'t realise how my life was changing. When I was 17, 18, 20, I didn\'t realise how big football was and everything around football. How many people live for football and love football. I was a professional, but I was a supporter."', '"Life,Love,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The Premier League is very difficult football and very different to when you play in Europe, but the player has to have experience to adapt, and this is the key point."', '"Experience,Football,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When I retire, the only thing that concerns me is that no one can say that I was a bad team-mate or disrespectful or self-important."', '"Me,Bad,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Liverpool is a fundamental part of my life. They don\'t remember me that way, but time will change that. I could not have chosen a better place to go when I left Atletico."', '"Life,Change,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I want to say thanks to the Chelsea fans because I have seen them very, very happy with me for joining Chelsea."', '"Me,Fans,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The Champions League is a big ambition, and all the footballers want to play in it; it is a very important competition."', '"Competition,Ambition,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I remember when I first came to Liverpool, Pepe Reina helped with everything, and he made it easy for me. When I was Atletico Madrid captain, I tried to help everyone. These are the basics in football: you need to create an atmosphere and try to create a group of friends. It\'s not easy, and it doesn\'t always happen, but you have to try."', '"Football,Me,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The biggest ambition in my career is still to win the European Cup. I want to have a picture of that to look at later; I want to have that medal. You can have a contract that is better than your friends, but no player looks back and says: \'I won more money.\'"', '"Money,Look,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Liverpool is a massive club in reputation, but as soon as I came here, it felt like Atletico to me. It is a working city, an honest city. The people work all week, and on Saturday they want to go to Anfield and watch the best team in the world."', '"Work,Best,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"You have to know what club you are playing for, or you just play for yourself. Every time I put on a Liverpool shirt, I know it is more than just a football game."', '"Time,Football,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"One of the reasons I chose to come to Liverpool was because of the mentality of the club. It\'s a working club and a working city. I don\'t know why, but I feel like one of the people here. They recognise me and wish me luck, but in Spain, they surround you and you can\'t do anything. I think they\'re happy with me here."', '"Me,City,Luck"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"My baby will be growing up in Liverpool, so we have another Scouser."', '"Will,Baby,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"After winning the European Championship with Spain, I know exactly how it feels to win a major trophy, and I know that, if we can win at Liverpool, it will feel the same or even better than it did with Spain."', '"Winning,Better,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"At Liverpool, I had almost everything but titles. I felt like a king, but the team was falling apart."', '"King,Falling,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"If the manager thinks there is another player better than you, he is going to play, and this is the way. You have to try to improve and keep fighting and try to change the manager\'s mind."', '"Change,Mind,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Everything I have done in my career I have done from my values and doing things the way I like to do. So winning doesn\'t matter the world for me.', '"Me,World,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Messi is the best. I have not seen or will ever see a player like Lionel Messi.', '"Best,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When young players become one of the best in the world, everyone wants to sign them."', '"Best,World,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"If we win the Champions League, everyone is a better, more recognised player, but if you win an individual award and nothing with your team, it means nothing."', '"Award,Better,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"If we win trophies, we have the chance to win individual awards because it comes with the team targets."', '"Chance,Win,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I\'m a quiet guy, but on the pitch, it\'s different. You have to do everything you can to win and help your teammates."', '"Win,Help,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I was always fighting with everyone when I was a kid. I was playing with people two or three years older than me, and I had to survive. So I love the physical game, the contact. And I don\'t know why, but I think football is like this. It is not just touching the ball and stringing together 50 pretty passes consecutively."', '"Love,Football,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"For me, Real Madrid are just like any other club, like Barcelona, Milan, Bayern Munich, or Inter. Just another big club."', '"Me,Real,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I just do not see myself playing for Madrid. They do not attract me, especially because of my past with Atletico."', '"Myself,Me,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Ronaldo is different from Messi. He is very impressive down the wings.', '"Wings,Down,He"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When you play, you do not ask yourself how it feels to be on the bench. You have to live it to understand how difficult it is to be there without being there. To enter a match knowing you do not have the confidence of the coach. To play when you simply don\'t have the habit of playing."', '"Confidence,Yourself,Habit"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"A player wants to be remembered for what he has won, for the medals, for what he has given his club."', '"Medals,Club,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"You can have a contract that is better than your friends, but no player looks back and says, \'I won more money.\'"', '"Money,Better,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'It was very hard to go through life as a small boy supporting Atletico.', '"Life,Boy,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"My father worked every day; my brother and sister had to travel many hours to study, so Atletico were for people like us."', '"Travel,Day,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I left in Liverpool a lot of friends. I have a very good relationship with all of them.', '"Relationship,Good,Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'My only path has always been to work hard.', '"Work,Path,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The Premier League is tough because, as soon as you lose a couple of games, you\'re out of the race for the league."', '"Lose,Tough,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'You always have to aspire to everything; winning titles is what I\'ve been missing. And I will give my life and everything I have in order to achieve it.', '"Life,My Life,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"English football has an enormous following across the world, not just because of the players but because of its history, its tradition, the excitement, the capacity crowds."', '"History,Football,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Atleti fans always demand your all on the field, and I guarantee that I will give them that and more."', '"Fans,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'No one has given me anything for free.', '"Me,Free,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Domestic titles are very important, but to win the Champions League, you are saying, \'We are the best team in Europe.\'"', '"Best,Win,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The worst part about not playing is when you think that you are ready to do it. You try to get more minutes, taking the chances, but you end up in a situation where things have not gone well for you for weeks - or for years. That is like swimming wet clothes."', '"Swimming,Situation,End"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When I was a boy, I was really thin, small, long-haired. I always looked young. People thought, \'He can\'t play football.\' I used that to my advantage."', '"Football,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Each player has one place in the world where he is happy, and as a result, he plays well. My place is Anfield. Every game I can play there, I feel good."', '"Good,Feel Good,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I always live in the present. I never dream about what might happen. Why? It might not.', '"Live,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"As a kid, I never once dreamt of playing for Liverpool."', '"Never,Once,Playing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I have good memories and bad memories of games against Chelsea. All the goals are good memories because all of them are special.', '"Good,Memories,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"When I played against Chelsea, there was always a big motivation because it was a special game; it was always one of the biggest games of the season. This is one of the reasons why I wanted to join Chelsea: because I want to be part of this kind of team."', '"Game,Big,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Football is not a sport populated by honest people. You can\'t tell the truth or be up front with people. It\'s a business, and no one is friends."', '"Truth,Business,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I had the best three years of my career at Liverpool.', '"Best,Three,Liverpool"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Real Madrid is like Manchester United or Liverpool or Bayern Munich. There is so much history, and you need to play and win against that history. It\'s difficult to play against them because you fight against everything - the history, the players - but because of that, the motivation is always so high."', '"History,Fight,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"The MLS is a fantastic competition, and it is growing all the time."', '"Time,Competition,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'I had team-mates who didn\'t care if the team won or lost because they were not playing. I never wanted to be like that.', '"Care,Lost,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"In the dressing room, you can never lose that group concept."', '"Lose,Never,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I learnt that if we won, it didn\'t matter that I hadn\'t played. I had to keep working."', '"Matter,Keep,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"I am a professional, and I always fulfil my deals."', '"I Am,Always,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"Liverpool had a lot of success under Rafa Benitez, and that is difficult for anyone to follow."', '"Success,Difficult,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', '"At Liverpool, winning is customary."', '"Winning,Liverpool"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Chelsea gave me what I was looking for when I left Liverpool trophies. I\'ll always see it as a success.', '"Success,Me,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3c', 'Liverpool was a special city that took to me; I will always remember how special that place was. I obviously don\'t miss the rain.', '"Rain,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'Risk is to do something that 99 percent of the time would be a failure.', '"Failure,Time,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"For me to go to a restaurant and eat something that is not only good, but totally new, is a double thrill. Double the enjoyment."', '"Good,Restaurant,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'I am not a multimillionaire. I don\'t own a yacht or a Ferrari. I live in a 60-square- metre flat. My needs are simple.', '"Simple,I Am,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'Everywhere the sky is blue. There are a multitude of cuisines and dishes. I think of them as the languages and dialects of food.', '"Food,Sky,Blue"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'I don\'t worry about the things I can\'t change.', '"Change,Worry,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I wanted to take nouvelle cuisine further, to the point where we were breaking down the essence of taste and sensation, reconfiguring food as a series of really intense hits on the tongue."', '"Food,Down,Taste"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I never even dreamed of being a chef, and that\'s fundamental."', '"Chef,Never,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I believe that if you eat well, you work even better."', '"Work,Believe,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I had a very normal childhood, and my mother cooked very normal food."', '"Food,Childhood,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"If a child plays sport early in childhood, and doesn\'t give it up, he will play sport for the rest of his life. And if children have a connection with, and are involved in the preparation of, the food they eat, then it will be normal for them to cook these kind of meals, and they will go on cooking them for the rest of their lives."', '"Life,Food,Cooking"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'Ferran Adria making hamburgers... some thought it was crazy. But getting them perfect was a challenge. Plus I\'m fascinated by all aspects of food.', '"Food,Perfect,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"Innovation, being avant garde, is always polemic."', '"Innovation,Always,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I was 18 when I first started working at a restaurant. I was a dishwasher. I only got the job because I wanted to go to Ibiza for vacation, and washing dishes was the only job I could find."', '"Restaurant,Find,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"Friends are really important, especially when you\'ve had the successes that I\'ve had. I\'ve gone really far in my career, so they\'re the ones that keep you humble, keep your feet on the ground."', '"Humble,Feet,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I don\'t read books regularly, because I\'m always writing them. I\'ve written 30 books, thousands of pages."', '"Always,Because,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I cook more theoretically than I do practically. My job is creative, and in the kitchen, the biggest part of my creativity is theoretical."', '"Creativity,Kitchen,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"Why not mix this and that? If soy goes well with fish, how come no one does beef carpaccio with soy? Why do we have such a taste and not another? It\'s all about culture. There is something, however, that I really don\'t like: bell peppers."', '"Fish,Culture,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"In a city, it\'s very hard to do a restaurant, an avant-garde-cuisine restaurant, where each year you need to change the whole menu."', '"Change,Restaurant,City"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"We never have business meals at El Bulli. If it\'s about business, you\'re probably not paying much attention to the food."', '"Business,Food,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"If I were a customer, and I was given a dish with peppers, I would hate it. I also don\'t like blood sausage."', '"Hate,Blood,Customer"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"It\'s very hard to be an innovator at the highest level in any discipline. For some chefs it\'s merely about combining ingredients, but that\'s something you can do with your eyes closed."', '"Eyes,Discipline,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"When we\'re ill, one of the last things we have that we can enjoy is food."', '"Food,Enjoy,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"When people arrive at El Bulli, everybody goes through the kitchen. It\'s a way of making them feel at home. When they leave, the only thing I ask is whether they\'ve been happy. Everything in between, I don\'t particularly care."', '"Home,Care,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"When I was a teenager, my idol was the Dutch footballer Johan Cruyff. He\'s the only person I\'ve ever asked for an autograph."', '"Person,Footballer,Idol"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'I don\'t dream at night; life has given me the stuff I need to be able to dream during the day. I\'m very lucky.', '"Life,Night,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"I have a driver\'s licence, but the truth is that I hardly ever drive. I prefer to get around by taxi."', '"Truth,Drive,Truth Is"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'I can\'t live without activity; I can\'t be sedentary.', '"Live,Activity,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'Monkeys don\'t enjoy or appreciate flavours. Experts have told us that human beings are the only beings that can appreciate food at this higher level and the only living beings that cook.', '"Food,Living,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"There are many cultural prejudices. For instance, even though fresh fish is a regional staple, Catalans don\'t like sashimi."', '"Fish,Fresh,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', 'Just to eat is a gift.', '"Gift,Eat,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"Chefs have only been able to work in restaurants, high-end cuisine. Why? Why haven\'t they been able to find other scenarios? For those chefs who want to do avant-garde cuisine, should they be finding their income in a restaurant?"', '"Work,Restaurant,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3d', '"When you talk about avant-garde cuisine, the surprise factor is really important. For example, I love looking at blogs and the photos, but I\'m not that keen on other people taking photos of my dishes."', '"Love,Surprise,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Studying physics, mathematics, and chemistry is worshipping God."', '"God,Mathematics,Physics"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'My position on democracy is really clear. Any attempt to overthrow the country is a betrayal to our unity and is treason.', '"Democracy,Unity,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'Avoiding the physical sciences due to the fear that they will lead to heresy is childish.', '"Fear,Childish,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I consider myself an ordinary Muslim who is constantly working to put himself in the framework established by the Koran and the tradition of the Prophet Mohammed. I study the works of experts of jurisprudence, Koranic commentary, hadith commentary, and Sufism."', '"Myself,Tradition,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Erdogan thinks if he gets rid of me, he thinks ending me will end the movement. He couldn\'t be more wrong."', '"Me,Ending,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I think the United States is mindful of its reputation for its democracy and rule of law, and if they are willing to risk that reputation by extraditing me based on the request and claims made by Turkey, I would never say no. I would go willingly."', '"Democracy,Me,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I feel the pain of people who suffer in my own neurons and sometimes cannot even watch TV. It is impossible not to be worried. But I trust that however cruel treatment they receive, Hizmet sympathizers will continue to respect to the law and will remain peaceful."', '"Respect,Trust,Pain"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"If somebody who appears to be a Hizmet sympathizer has been involved in an attempted coup, he betrays my ideals."', '"He,Who,Somebody"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"We are mortals, we will die one day."', '"Day,Die,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I grew up in a humble family with a shy personality.', '"Family,Personality,Humble"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'The greater jihad is proclaiming war on our ego\'s destructive and negative emotions and thoughts... which prevent us from attaining perfection.', '"War,Thoughts,Perfection"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"My message is, if someone beats you, act like you don\'t have hands. If someone slurs you, act like you don\'t have a tongue. Society is already polarized enough, don\'t make it worse."', '"Society,Hands,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"A Turkey under a dictatorial regime, providing haven to violent radicals and pushing its Kurdish citizens into desperation, would be a nightmare for Middle East security."', '"Security,Desperation,Middle"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I have always tried to be a humble servant of God and a humble member of humanity.', '"God,Humble,Humanity"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"My philosophy - inclusive and pluralist Islam, dedicated to service to human beings from every faith - is antithetical to armed rebellion."', '"Faith,Service,Rebellion"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'The lesser jihad is our active fulfillment of Islam\'s commands and duties.', '"Active,Islam,Fulfillment"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I probably will not live to see Turkey become an exemplary democracy, but I pray that the downward authoritarian drift can be stopped before it is too late."', '"Democracy,Late,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'The principles and form of government that form the basis of democracy are compatible with Islamic values.', '"Government,Democracy,Principles"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"When the opportunities come, Cemaat participants, just like any other citizen will make their choices based on their values."', '"Will,Choices,Values"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"No citizen or social group can be completely isolated from politics, because policy decisions and actions affect their lives."', '"Politics,Group,Policy"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I have spent over 50 years preaching and teaching the values of peace, mutual respect and altruism."', '"Respect,Peace,Values"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"The noble position of motherhood aside, our general opinion about women is that, while taking into account their specific needs, it should be made possible for them to take on every role, including the jobs of physician, military officer, judge and president of a country."', '"Women,Country,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I would curse people who resort to coups against democracy, liberty, republic."', '"Democracy,People,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Regardless of their religious observance, citizens can and should unite around universal human rights and freedoms, and democratically oppose those who violate them."', '"Human Rights,Human,Universal"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"We invite our friends who hold high positions in the legislative branch of government and state institutions to master the skills of administration, so they could, when the time comes, reform the Turkish state and make it more fruitful at all its levels in the name of Islam."', '"Time,Government,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'Telling or encouraging people to vote for a party would be an insult to peoples\' intellect.', '"People,Insult,Vote"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"If I were to say anything to people I may say people should vote for those who are respectful to democracy, rule of law, who get on well with people."', '"Democracy,Law,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"My message to the Turkish people is never to view any military intervention positively because through military intervention, democracy cannot be achieved."', '"Democracy,View,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Under any circumstances, if I had to return to Turkey and face the gallows, I will not blink an eye."', '"Face,Will,Circumstances"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I don\'t see a bright future for Turkey. It pains me. But I have some hope, I pray for it to be better. It is a blessed country, a NATO member, and was an E.U. candidate. These were things we wanted."', '"Hope,Future,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I suffered during the military intervention of May 27, 1960, and then again on March 12, 1971 and again on September 12, 1980, and I was targeted February 28, 1997. My respect for the military aside, I have always been against interventions."', '"Respect,Always,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"In many places around the world, including Turkey until the 1950s, Muslims didn\'t have full freedom of religion. Even personal practice was not allowed, and they had to practice in secret."', '"Freedom,Religion,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'It is possible that people who share core values will make choices along the same lines.', '"People,Will,Choices"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'We will never be a part of any plot against those who are governing our country.', '"Country,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I have never imagined being or wished to be chosen as something important in the world.', '"World,Important,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Islam\'s basic principles of belief, worship, morality, and behavior are not affected by changing times. Islam does not propose a certain unchangeable form of government or attempt to shape it. Islam has never offered nor established a theocracy in its name."', '"Government,Behavior,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I cannot accept concepts such as Gulenism or Gulenist. I was only a writer and an official preacher among people. I can have no direct influence on any person or activity. It is inconceivable that I can exert pressure on anybody.', '"Influence,Pressure,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I have always been against coups, and I cursed them."', '"Always,Against,Cursed"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I am neither a sociologist nor a psychologist, but you don\'t have to be one to see that Turkey is in a vortex of problems, isolated from the world."', '"World,I Am,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Turkey is a diverse country... I think that democracy is the ideal system for a country with a social foundation such as this. My view is based on my belief that everyone should be able to comfortably live what they believe, and this is only possible in a truly democratic environment. I am insistent in my views and I strongly believe in what I say."', '"Democracy,View,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I even reject and condemn in the strongest terms the idea, the consideration of a military coup. If I had the chance I would stand in front of the people who would attempt such a thing and open my arms and beg them to stop."', '"Chance,People,Stand"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Even if, at the helm of the country there are people who would like to replace me and suppress me and oppress me at the level of blood-sucking vampires, then I do not want to remove them with anti-democratic means. This is my attitude toward any and even the idea of the consideration of a military coup."', '"Attitude,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Turkey initiated true multiparty elections in 1950 to join NATO. As a requirement of its membership, NATO can and should demand that Turkey honor its commitment to the alliance\'s democratic norms."', '"Honor,True,Commitment"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"Erdogan\'s persecution of his people is not simply a domestic matter. The ongoing pursuit of civil society, journalists, academics and Kurds in Turkey is threatening the long-term stability of the country."', '"Society,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'Profiling any segment of society and viewing them as a threat is a sign of intolerance.', '"Society,Intolerance,Sign"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I have always believed in seeking happiness in the happiness of others and the virtue of seeking God\'s pleasure in helping His people.', '"Happiness,God,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"I have said time and again that the republican order, and secularism, when executed perfectly, are blessings from God."', '"God,Time,Blessings"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', '"My core belief is to seek peace in the world, helping people eliminate certain malevolent attitudes through education as much as possible."', '"Education,Peace,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I don\'t have a need to promote myself.', '"Myself,Need,Promote"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I\'ve never sought to be known or recognized by people.', '"People,Never,Known"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'I simply share ideas I believe in with people around me.', '"Me,Believe,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('391965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd3e', 'Entrepreneurs and volunteers inspired by Hizmet\'s values have invested in modern education and community service in more than 150 countries.', '"Education,Community,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
