	('391994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I began revolution with 82 men. If I had to do it again, I do it with 10 or 15 and absolute faith. It does not matter how small you are if you have faith and plan of action."', '"Faith,Men,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
