	('392036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Mubarak was oppressing and pillaging his own people. He was an enemy to the Palestinians and an accomplice of Israel, the sixth nuclear power on the planet, associated with the war-mongering NATO group."', '"Power,People,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Reactionaries often describe both Marx and Lenin as theorists, without taking into consideration that their utopias inspired Russia and China - the two countries called upon to lead a new world which will allow for human survival if imperialism does not first unleash a criminal, exterminating war."', '"War,World,New"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
