	('392039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"We are political animals, as, not without reason, affirmed Aristotle, who perhaps influenced humanity\'s thinking more than any other ancient philosopher through his almost 200 treatises, according to reports, of which only 31 have been preserved."', '"Political,Thinking,Humanity"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
