	('392054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"At the age of 6, a teacher full of ambitions, who taught in the small public school of Biran, convinced my family that I should travel to Santiago de Cuba to accompany my older sister who would enter a highly prestigious convent school. Including me was a skill of that very teacher from the little school in Biran."', '"Family,Age,Teacher"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'I don\'t think anyone has been slandered more than the Jews.', '"More,Think,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The last time I visited Qaddafi was in May of 2001, 15 years after Reagan attacked his rather modest residence where he took me to show me how it had been left."', '"Time,Me,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Social struggles have been taking place throughout millennia, since human beings, by resorting to wars, were able to take hold of a surplus production to satisfy the essential needs of life."', '"Life,Place,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'Cynicism is something which has become symbolic of imperial policy.', '"Policy,Something,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The Revolution did not assume a socialist nature because of support from the U.S.S.R.; it was the other way around: support from the U.S.S.R. was produced by the socialist nature of the Cuban Revolution. To such a degree, that when the U.S.S.R. disappears, Cuba keeps on being socialist."', '"Nature,Support,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The United States never stopped conspiring against the Arab world, which holds the largest oil reserves on the planet."', '"World,Never,Oil"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'Defending peace is the duty of all.', '"Peace,Duty,Defending"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'I see Libya as a member of the Non-Aligned Movement and a sovereign State of the nearly 200 members of the United Nations.', '"See,United Nations,I See"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Experience acquired in the heroic battle against Batista\'s tyranny showed that the enemy, no matter what his strength, could not defeat the Cuban people."', '"Strength,Experience,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The world has not yet reached the point which, in my view, is an essential condition for the survival of our human species: access by all the peoples to the material resources of this planet."', '"View,World,Survival"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"To our brothers in Latin America and the world, we must convey that the Cuban people will overcome."', '"World,America,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I will never retire from politics, the revolution, or the ideas I have."', '"Politics,Will,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"At times, I\'ve referred to Christ\'s miracles, and have said, \'Well, Christ multiplied the fish and the loaves to feed the people. That is precisely what we want to do with the Revolution and socialism.\'"', '"Fish,People,Socialism"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'Cuba came to be the last country to get rid of Spanish colonialism and the first to shake off the heinous imperialist tutelage.', '"Country,Colonialism,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"In my next incarnation, I want to be a writer."', '"Next,Want,Writer"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The Soviet Union, the socialist camp, the People\'s Republic of China, and North Korea helped us resist, with essential supplies and weapons, the implacable blockade of the United States, the most powerful empire ever to exist."', '"People,Us,Soviet Union"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The U.S.S.R. had absolutely nothing to do with the triumph of the Cuban Revolution.', '"Nothing,Revolution,Triumph"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Chinese combatants, men and women, inheritors of a millennial culture, are people of uncommon intelligence and an invincible spirit of struggle."', '"Women,Men,Intelligence"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"My idea, as the whole world knows, is that the capitalist system now doesn\'t work either for the United States or the world, driving it from crisis to crisis, which are each time more serious."', '"Work,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Every country must be absolutely free to adopt the type of economic, political and social system that it considers convenient."', '"Political,Free,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'What prevails in every corner of this globalized world is the real struggle of our species for its own survival.', '"Struggle,World,Survival"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'I was not the son of a worker or lacking in material or social resources for a relatively comfortable existence; I could say I miraculously escaped wealth.', '"Wealth,Son,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"As we know, while our species remains alive, everybody has the sacred duty to be optimistic. Ethically, any other behaviour wouldn\'t be admissible."', '"Alive,Duty,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'None of us has any personal interest above the interests of the country. Our country is more important than our careers.', '"Country,Important,More"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'I am a just man.', '"Man,I Am,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Following the missile crisis, detente started to gain ground between the United States and the Soviet Union, so the international political climate improved after that."', '"Political,Climate,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Some time ago, the United States was an English colony. If an Englishman were asked if the United States would be independent, he would have said no, that it would always be an English colony."', '"Time,Independent,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"During the second half of the twentieth century, I had the privilege of living through years of intensive erudition, and I realized that Canadians, located in the northernmost region of this hemisphere, were always respectful towards our country."', '"Country,Living,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Every citizen has the real right to receive general education and professional training at no cost, something that the United States has not been able to ensure for all its inhabitants."', '"Education,Training,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"We are proud of the history of our country; we learned it in school and have grown up hearing of freedom, justice and human rights."', '"Freedom,History,Justice"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The Cuban model doesn\'t even work for us anymore.', '"Work,Us,Even"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"It is a fundamental principle of criminal law that an imputed offense must correspond exactly to the type of crime described by law. If no law applies exactly to the point in question, then there is no offense."', '"Law,Point,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I have always fought for concrete facts, for justice."', '"Justice,Facts,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"We have always been prepared to negotiate with the U.S. government everything that has to do with bilateral relations, on a basis of the strictest mutual respect for the sovereign rights of each country. We will never try to ask the government of the United States to change its economic and political system."', '"Change,Respect,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'There is nothing that compares to the Holocaust.', '"Nothing,Holocaust,Compares"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"England was the first true colonial power to use its dominion over a large part of Africa, the Middle East, Asia, Australia, North America, and many Caribbean islands, in the first half of the 20th century."', '"Power,America,True"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"General Giap was one of the most brilliant military strategists of our era, who in Dien Bien Phu was able to place missile launchers in remote, mountainous jungles, something the yankee and European military officers considered impossible."', '"Impossible,Place,Brilliant"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"There is plenty of building material and more than enough manpower to make a decent home for every Cuban. But if we continue to wait for the golden calf, a thousand years will have gone by, and the problem will remain the same."', '"Home,Wait,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"When the Revolution triumphed in 1959, our island was a true Yankee colony. The United States had duped and disarmed our Liberation Army. One couldn\'t speak of developed agriculture, but of immense plantations exploited on the base of manual and animal labour that in general used neither fertilizers nor machinery."', '"Agriculture,True,Animal"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'We do not need the empire to give us anything.', '"Anything,Need,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Peoples do not defy repression and death, nor do they remain for nights on end protesting energetically, just because of merely formal matters."', '"Death,End,Just Because"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"On one occasion, I accompanied my father to Pinares de Mayari. I was eight or nine years old. How he enjoyed talking when he left the house in Biran! There he was the proprietor of the land where sugar cane, pasture, and other agricultural crops were planted."', '"Father,Sugar,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Without a tutor to help me in the study of Marxism-Leninism, I was no more than a theorist and, of course, had total confidence in the Soviet Union."', '"Confidence,Me,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I don\'t think it is so difficult to solve the problems between Cuba and the United States; it all depends on whether there is a dialogue, a discussion, or if the prejudices and hatred of people like the extremists and terrorists from the Cuban community, who try to impose their policies, prevail."', '"Community,Problems,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Senator McCain is Israel\'s most unconditional ally in Mossad\'s machinations, something that even his worst adversaries would have been able to imagine. McCain participated alongside this secret service in the creation of the Islamic State, which has appropriated a considerable part of Iraq as well as a third of Syria, according to its affirmations."', '"Service,Worst,Creation"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The kings of Spain brought us the conquistadores and masters, whose footprints remained in the circular land grants assigned to those searching for gold in the sands of rivers, an abusive and shameful form of exploitation, traces of which can be noted from the air in many places around the country."', '"Gold,Country,Air"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I never saw a contradiction between the ideas that sustain me and the ideas of that symbol, of that extraordinary figure, Jesus Christ."', '"Me,Jesus Christ,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'NATO\'s brutal military alliance has become the most perfidious instrument of repression known in the history of humankind.', '"History,Alliance,Instrument"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The squandering of oil and gas is associated with one of the greatest tragedies, not in the least resolved, which is suffered by humankind: climate change."', '"Change,Climate,Climate Change"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"For revolutionary Cubans, to cooperate with other poor and exploited peoples has always been a political principle and a duty towards humanity."', '"Political,Humanity,Duty"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The people respect and believe in men who fulfill their duty.', '"Respect,Men,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Any negotiated, peaceful solution to the problems between the United States and peoples, or any people of Latin America, which does not imply force or the use of force, must be addressed in accordance with international principles and norms."', '"Problems,America,People"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Our Revolution emerged where it was least expected by the empire, in a hemisphere where it was used to acting like an all-powerful master."', '"Acting,Revolution,Master"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'Even Gaddafi\'s adversaries assure us that he stood out for his intelligence as a student; he was expelled from high-school for his anti-monarchic activities. He managed to enroll in another high-school and later graduated in law at the University of Benghazi at the age of 21.', '"Age,Intelligence,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The prestige of the international financial institutions rates less than zero.', '"Institutions,Financial,Zero"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'I almost laughed about the Machiavellian plans of the presidents of the United States.', '"Plans,About,Almost"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I was born in a territory called Biran, in the eastern region of Cuba. It\'s known by that name, although it has never appeared on a map."', '"Name,Never,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"None of us is designed for the role we must assume in a revolutionary society, although Cubans had the privilege of Jose Marti\'s example."', '"Society,Privilege,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The universities are available only to those who share my revolutionary beliefs.', '"Only,Who,Available"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Nature teaches us that tens of billions of light years may have passed, and life in all of its expressions has always been subjected to an incredible combination of matter and radiation."', '"Life,Nature,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'Our position is that we do not accept conditions of any kind which may affect the independence and sovereignty of our country just with the view to solve economic problems existing between the United States and Cuba.', '"Independence,View,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Marx and Engels never talked about murdering the bourgeois. According to the old bourgeois concept, the judges were the ones who judged, and the executioners were the ones who executed."', '"Never,Old,Judges"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Even in the United States, the enslavement of African descendants continued until the presidency of Abraham Lincoln. That brutal form of slavery was abolished there hardly thirty years before it was abolished in Cuba."', '"Even,United,Before"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"I barely need to reiterate what you already know: the close links that exist between our people and the people of Venezuela and Hugo Chavez, the promoter of the Bolivarian Revolution and the United Socialist Party he founded."', '"People,Know,Revolution"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Many things shall change in Cuba, but they shall change because of our efforts and despite the United States. Perhaps that empire shall crumble first."', '"Change,Because,First"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The unyielding resistance of the Cuban patriots is symbolized by our 5 Heroes. They shall never back down! They shall never surrender!', '"Back,Never,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Never have we stolen the intelligences of other peoples. On the contrary, in Cuba we have trained tens of thousands of doctors and other top-level professionals, for free, in order to send them back to their own countries."', '"Free,Back,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"The death of Abdel Nasser on September 28, 1970, was an irreversible setback for Egypt."', '"Death,Egypt,September"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', 'The United States is supplying the most modern and sophisticated weaponry to Israel to the tune of billions of dollars every year.', '"Year,Sophisticated,Israel"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd40', '"Born to a tribal Bedouin family of nomadic desert shepherds in the region of Tripoli, Gaddafi was profoundly anti-colonialist. It is affirmed that his paternal grandfather died fighting against the Italian invaders when Libya was invaded by them in 1911."', '"Family,Fighting,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I am training a lot harder, gym a lot, more muscle, strengthening my back, my legs, my muscles, my weak areas a lot."', '"I Am,Training,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'One of my aims is to be the fastest and regarded as the best fast bowler in the world.', '"Best,World,Fast"', '2023-05-29 11:43:00', '2023-05-29 11:43:00'),
	('392127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I love to play Test cricket; it\'s the main cricket.', '"Love,Cricket,Test"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"Taking part and helping West Indies win the World T20 in 2012 - I\'ll never forget the feeling. The celebrations afterwards were crazy, a massive all-nighter."', '"World,Crazy,Never Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I found it quite funny when my teacher at secondary school saw me bowl and wanted me to throw the javelin. So I tried, and I kept hitting the back of my head!"', '"Funny,Teacher,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I do enjoy batting - if the bowling\'s not quick!', '"Enjoy,Batting,Quick"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'The late Runako Morton had some pretty dodgy clothes.', '"Late,Clothes,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'Being selected for West Indies actually changed my life.', '"Life,My Life,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I haven\'t tried to model myself on anyone. I have my own action, and that suits me."', '"Myself,Me,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I try to keep the ball up to the bat, and I usually get the ball to outswing, so I get wickets like that."', '"Bat,Ball,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I don\'t bowl to hit people; I bowl to get wickets.', '"People,Get,Bowl"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"My first love is football. When I get the chance, I play football for fitness."', '"Love,Fitness,Chance"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I\'m delighted to have signed for such an ambitious club as Hampshire. I\'m very much looking forward to my first taste of county cricket. It\'s also an honour to follow other Bajans like Malcolm Marshall and Gordon Greenidge to Hampshire.', '"Looking Forward,Cricket,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"God is good, and my health is in his hands."', '"God,Health,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"You have to be smart on your feet. It will be hard on wickets where the ball will keep low. Hopefully, you can get one to fly, and that puts doubts in the batsman\'s mind."', '"Fly,Mind,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'My aim has always been to be at the top.', '"Aim,Always,Top"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I was away from the game for a few years, and it feels good to be back. I\'m bowling quite well and also getting the ball to reverse swing. During the time off, I worked a lot on getting the ball to reverse swing; now it\'s working well for me."', '"Time,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I did a lot of good work with my trainer and the physio in Barbados, and they were tremendous help to me during my comeback period."', '"Work,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I have some goals I\'m looking to achieve, and one thing is to help the team win and move back up the ladder. This is vitally important to the team overall and to the supporters of West Indies cricket."', '"Goals,Cricket,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"I felt I bowled well for Barbados, and that helped me."', '"Me,Well,Felt"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'It is good to make my comeback in Jamaica after not playing for so long.', '"Good,Comeback,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"For me, David Warner isn\'t just the future of Australian batting, he\'s the future for cricket in general because he can excel in any form of the game. I\'m excited just watching him."', '"Future,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I played cricket at primary school but hardly at all at high school. I was more of a footballer.', '"Cricket,School,Footballer"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I like to let the ball do the talking.', '"Ball,Talking,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'Any win is good for a team that has been losing.', '"Good,Win,Losing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'Test cricket should be No. 1 for every cricketer.', '"Cricket,Test,Every"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"In Twenty20s, you have to bowl a lot fuller, especially at the death, and you\'ve got to be mindful of what you\'re doing. But it\'s still cricket."', '"Death,Cricket,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'A team needs experienced cricketers to guide its younger players.', '"Players,Guide,Needs"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', '"It is going to be difficult for the West Indies to get back to the top, but we got to start somewhere, and if playing young players is the way we have decided to go, these young players must be given the chance to mature and develop and not be discarded at an early age."', '"Age,Chance,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd41', 'I don\'t have any complaints. I cannot say I miss playing for the West Indies that much.', '"Cannot,Say,Miss"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"He always scores the opening goal. Because it is one thing to score 30 goals with hat-tricks in easy wins, and another that 20 of those 30 goals are enough to win 1-0. Nobody does that as well as Diego Costa."', '"Goals,Win,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I\'ve had some of the best years of my career at Atletico and remember the supporters, my teammates, and the coaching staff fondly."', '"Best,Remember,Teammates"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Neymar and Hazard are amazing talents, but the player who gave me most trophies was Diego Costa."', '"Amazing,Me,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'In one year I won two titles - one being the Premier League. I have a trophy at home that not many people have and in possibly the most competitive league in the world.', '"Home,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"When Atletico tried to buy me back, I did everything I could to make it possible. I had offers from clubs in France and Italy, but I would not have left Chelsea for any other side - only for Atletico Madrid."', '"Me,Back,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'In the Premier League the big clubs can lose and drop points. Games that are supposed to be easy are never easy.', '"Lose,Never,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'I was delighted when I found out that Atletico wanted to take me back. It\'s the best thing that could have happened to me.', '"Best,Me,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I\'m always in the \'butcher\' role. But the only way to stop Messi one-on-one is to foul him. Otherwise, if I\'m alone, I\'ll only get the ball one in 20 times. I have to use other weapons, I know the best way to stop him. I know he does not like playing with his back to goal, you must be right on top of him when he gets the ball."', '"Alone,Best,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Paulinho will surprise many people. If he does not fit at Barca, he would at Atletico."', '"Surprise,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"You know \'The Shawshank Redemption?\' I\'ve seen that movie, like, 30 times or something. \'Dirty Harry,\' too - I love that movie."', '"Love,Dirty,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I watch a lot of movies, and sometimes I watch the same ones a lot of times, so you get to learn a lot of words that way."', '"Movies,Words,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I lived in Holland for one year when I was younger and, although they speak Dutch there, I learned a little bit of English while I was there, but really I learned from movies and TV series like \'24\' and \'Prison Break.\'"', '"Movies,Prison,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Some players benefit from criticism, but for others, they don\'t."', '"Criticism,Others,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'I consider my time with Chelsea a personal triumph.', '"Time,Chelsea,Personal"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Often, players talk when they feel they are not being valued as they deserve. Then they get more attention."', '"Feel,Deserve,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Messi is so good that he can win La Liga even with a mediocre team, which is not the case. Barca remain up top every year because of him."', '"Good,Win,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'Epic things happen in soccer.', '"Things Happen,Things,Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"At the level Neymar moves at, you do not change teams for money."', '"Change,Money,Level"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'Everything can happen in football.', '"Football,Everything,Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Speaking about Mourinho is always controversial, and there\'s always some intrigue surrounding him. But he is an awesome coach who tries to take the maximum from each and every one of his players."', '"Always,Awesome,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I feel at home in Madrid. I have always felt important, wanted, and trusted by everyone here."', '"Home,Feel,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"When I left for Chelsea, I wanted to prove that I could play in the Premier League, but it didn\'t happen the way I dreamed."', '"Way,Prove,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Everyone wants to play. If you don\'t, normally you\'re not happy."', '"Happy,Everyone,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"When you work with Mourinho, you have to know that the group, the collective is above the individual."', '"Work,Know,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"It\'s true I wasn\'t as important at Chelsea. I never demanded that. What I wanted was to be a champion, because few people get that. I succeeded. But the happiness wasn\'t there."', '"Happiness,Champion,True"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"If you give Messi a metre, he\'ll snatch the ball and leave you behind."', '"Leave,Behind,Ball"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Many players enter the pitch just to change shirts, but I don\'t."', '"Change,Players,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'I hope I can retire at Atletico Madrid.', '"Hope,I Can,Retire"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"At Atleti, you get to be at a club which is growing all the time. I don\'t believe there is any better club."', '"Time,Believe,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Wherever Mourinho goes, he is a champion."', '"Champion,Wherever,He"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"Playing with Coutinho is easy. He\'s a very quick player who dribbles well. He knows how to play out wide, and my job is not just to go past and help him: it\'s also to give the greatest number of passes to him in space around the opposition right-back."', '"Space,Past,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"In Spain you fight, of course, against Real Madrid and Barcelona, and they almost never lose because they have the biggest squads, and they are two of the biggest clubs in the world. So it\'s really difficult."', '"Fight,World,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"When I arrived at Chelsea, I had got used to playing 50 games, and suddenly, I was sharing my position with another player."', '"Sharing,Position,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"When you\'re not playing, sometimes you\'re not full of confidence."', '"Confidence,Sometimes,Playing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'It\'s not easy playing against Barcelona in the Champions League. They are a club with a lot of history.', '"History,Easy,Club"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"With regards to the fans, whenever I\'ve played in the Atletico shirt, I have given all that I can. I think I will win the fans back on the field and not with words."', '"Words,Shirt,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', 'The Ballon d\'Or is a subjective matter.', '"Matter,Subjective"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I admire Messi: he\'s never complained to me in any game we played, but I\'ve also never asked him for his jersey and never would. I came to win, not to say I played against Messi."', '"Me,Game,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"A footballer\'s career is very short, and I want to finish it in a strong and spectacular way."', '"Way,Finish,Footballer"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd43', '"I have always liked Chelsea a lot. I watch a lot of the Premier League, and it is a club where you can feel the warmth of the fans."', '"Feel,Fans,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', 'I propose to build for eternity.', '"Build,Eternity,Propose"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', 'The gifts given to us by God must not be relinquished to those who speak ill of them and who are moved by envy or ignorance.', '"God,Ignorance,Envy"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', 'Do not share your inventions with many; share them only with the few who understand and love the sciences.', '"Love,Understand,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', '"We must not show to all and sundry the secrets of the waters flowing in ocean and river, or the devices that work on these waters. Let there be convened a council of experts and masters in mechanical art to deliberate what is needed to compose and construct these works."', '"Work,Art,River"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', 'To disclose too much of one\'s inventions and achievements is one and the same thing as to give up the fruit of one\'s ingenuity.', '"Fruit,Too Much,Same Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd44', '"Many are ready, when listening to the inventor, to belittle and deny his achievements so that he will no longer be heard in honourable places, but after some months or a year, they use the inventor\'s words in speech or writing or design."', '"Design,Words,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'What can you say about Carlo Ancelotti? I talk to him regularly and he made history for Milan.', '"History,Talk,He"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Who doesn\'t fight cannot play for my Milan.', '"Fight,Cannot,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I cried when I won but never when I lost.', '"Lost,Never,Won"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"In fact, the sense of positioning, anticipation, is something very natural. I always knew where the ball was going to drop."', '"Always,Anticipation,Ball"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'He is better than me in everything. I can only learn from Simone: he is a modern coach and seeing his Lazio side is a spectacle.', '"Me,Better,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Milan\'s fans follow me with great affection.', '"Great,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I always choose for the good of the team.', '"Good,Always,Choose"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Milan have faith in the man as well as in the player. They know that I will never be a burden to them.', '"Faith,Man,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"It is best to keep a substitution open for the final 15 minutes, as you never know if you are going to lose someone to injury and be left with 10 men."', '"Best,Men,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"When a player leaves, it means all the parties involved took this decision."', '"Decision,Means,Involved"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"The toughest defenders I\'ve faced are Alessandro Nesta, Paolo Maldini, Ivan Cordoba, Ciro Ferrara and Walter Samuel."', '"Defenders,Samuel,Toughest"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Without doubt the striker who resembles me the most is Alberto Gilardino, but also Paloschi."', '"Me,Doubt,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"With Cristiano Ronaldo, who is the best player in the world, Juventus are the best team in Europe or at least one of the best teams."', '"Best,World,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'My dream is to stay at AC Milan for my entire career.', '"Stay,Dream,Milan"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Racism at the stadium should be ignored, it is not right that this minority are given so much attention."', '"Attention,Right,Minority"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I want to end my career at Milan.', '"End,Want,Milan"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Pirlo is an irreplaceable player.', '"Irreplaceable,Player"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I cannot see Kaka wearing another jersey. He is loved by everyone here and he adores the environment at Milan.', '"See,Everyone,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I miss everything. The field, the dressing room, the training. I miss San Siro. But I was lucky enough to experience good feelings as a player."', '"Experience,Good,Training"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"As a player, I started in Serie C and got to the top of Europe and the world."', '"World,Europe,Top"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I look back on my career with pleasure.', '"Look,Back,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Overall I have always had my chances to play at Milan and I never thought about leaving.', '"Never,Always,Leaving"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I\'ve always thought that the best answers you can give are answers on the pitch, and I hope to continue doing just that, which is the most important thing."', '"Best,Hope,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'It is not easy to play three games in a week.', '"Three,Easy,Week"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'On a personal level I would like to reach Gerd Muller\'s European goal record.', '"Reach,Personal,Level"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I am very proud to be playing for Milan. It\'s always a privilege for me.', '"Me,I Am,Proud"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"At Milanello there isn\'t a particular atmosphere, we just want to do well."', '"Well,Atmosphere,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"When you\'re a kid your dream is to be decisive in a Champions League final, and I managed to do that."', '"Your,Dream,Final"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'A footballer must quit at the right time.', '"Time,Quit,Footballer"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I have to say that clubs like Piacenza, Atalanta, and Parma always call me, they make me feel important. Probably they also appreciated me as a man, not just as a player. But after everything I\'ve experienced with the Rossoneri\'s shirt, I think it\'s right that I end my career at Milan."', '"Man,Me,Shirt"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'It does not get better than scoring in a Champions League final.', '"Better,Final,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'What is the most important moment in my career? The Champions League final played in Athens in 2007 when I netted a double.', '"Moment,Important,Final"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I read criticism that I change the starting XI a lot, but I cannot play injured players."', '"Change,Criticism,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I am ambitious.', '"I Am,Ambitious,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I have a great relationship with Conte.', '"Relationship,Great,Great Relationship"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'It makes me proud if my players are called up the national team.', '"Me,Proud,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '150 goals? It\'s nice.', '"Goals,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Sometimes I play, sometimes I don\'t, when I\'m given the chance I try to be ready."', '"Chance,Sometimes,Ready"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"My team mates are fundamental for my characteristics, if they send in crosses I can play inside the area."', '"I Can,Inside,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"If you are not born a Ronaldo or a Kaka, you can still become a great player through commitment, serenity, perseverance, loving what you do."', '"Great,Perseverance,Serenity"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'You can learn from every match.', '"Match,Learn,Every"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I prepare everything in the tiniest detail. My diet, how I train. This has been my secret."', '"Diet,Everything,Detail"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Each of us has something which is our own and which only you yourself can pass on to others.', '"Yourself,Own,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'All the affection I feel around me helps me to keep working harder.', '"Me,Feel,Affection"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'My secret is passion.', '"Passion,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Both were wonderful experiences, but I\'ve always said the Champions League campaign where I was most important was 2003. However, the one the fans remember is 2007, which shows how important goals in a final are."', '"Goals,Remember,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'As a footballer I think your own history speaks for itself.', '"History,Own,Footballer"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I have the best job in the world. I think that\'s what the younger players need to learn.', '"Best,World,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'It\'s difficult to take in but my relationship with Milan is special.', '"Relationship,Difficult,Special"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'If you don\'t score for a few games at Juve you are immediately under scrutiny.', '"Score,Few,Scrutiny"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I know the respect Mourinho has for me.', '"Respect,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I always want to improve.', '"Always,Want,Improve"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Anyone who works makes mistakes and if you don\'t work, you never make mistakes."', '"Work,Mistakes,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I live to knock the ball into the back of the net.', '"Live,Back,Ball"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"It\'s fine by me, even if I score with my hand."', '"Me,Fine,Score"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I had a great time at Juventus, I have won a lot and I have scored a lot."', '"Time,Great,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I love it at the San Siro.', '"Love,I Love,San"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I am very happy to coach AC Milan, it\'s a very big opportunity for me because Milan is the club of my life."', '"Life,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'My dream is to be with AC Milan - I just hope to put them back on top.', '"Hope,Back,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"When a big club takes the lead at home, then they cannot let it slip and be turned over."', '"Home,Big,Club"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"A good coach is one who realises what he could have done better, and when you lose, it\'s the responsibility of the coach."', '"Good,Lose,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Who would not be emotional about everything that\'s been written about me?', '"Me,Everything,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Whatever Milan tell me to do, I will do."', '"Me,Will,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Carlo Ancelotti is a role model for me.', '"Me,Role Model,Role"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I think for a coach the most important thing is to have the players on your side.', '"Important,Your,Side"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I will always forgive a technical error, but I will never forgive the wrong attitude."', '"Attitude,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"My mother knows how to cook for me. If I lived abroad, I couldn\'t enjoy her meals."', '"Me,Mother,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Maybe that\'s my only remorse, not having played more alongside Ibrahmovic towards the end of my career with Milan. We had an incredible feeling - he was delighted when I scored and I think we were made to play together and be a strike partnership."', '"Together,End,More"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I\'ve scored five goals in the most important three finals, and we won all of them."', '"Goals,Important,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"It was very difficult in 2007. I was out for a long time after an ankle operation in Antwerp, then when I returned, I was not at my best, of course."', '"Best,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Everybody\'s going to be watching us, but I hope to lead Venezia into Serie A."', '"Hope,Watching,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I want to thank Milan because the most beautiful years of my life were spent wearing that shirt.', '"Life,Most Beautiful,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Balotelli is an asset for Italian football.', '"Football,Asset,Italian"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'When I won I always was part of a real team with real men and a real coach.', '"Men,Real,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"I\'ve scored quite a few times in Europe, but scoring in the Champions League final is something special."', '"Special,Europe,Something Special"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Soccer is my life.', '"Life,My Life,Soccer"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"A derby is different, it is not to be played, it is to be won!"', '"Different,Derby,Won"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I didn\'t have everything served to me on a silver platter during my career; unfair criticism helped me.', '"Me,Criticism,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'We\'re Milan and we\'re not afraid of anyone.', '"Afraid,Milan,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I have always said that to remain at a certain level we must always give our all.', '"Always,Said,Level"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I had some misunderstandings with Allegri but they have been cleared up.', '"Up,Had,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'From every coach that has coached me I have learnt something.', '"Me,Something,Coach"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'Life is made of cycles.', '"Life,Made,Cycles"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"No player is happy when he is substituted, I would be worried if it was the opposite."', '"Happy,He,Opposite"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"It\'s true that after spending as long as I have at the highest level, a number of injuries have nearly wrecked my career along the way."', '"Long,True,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I consider myself lucky because I\'ve had the possibility in life to do the one thing closest to my heart: playing football. I\'ve also been lucky enough to win prestigious trophies like two Champions Leagues and other competitions with Milan.', '"Life,Myself,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"After all the good years in the kit, I hope to close my career with Milan."', '"Hope,Good,Close"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'AC Milan are my top priority and I will never cause any problems for this team.', '"Problems,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"It would have been a shame not to reach 300 appearances with Milan, after 12 years as a Rossonero and 126 goals."', '"Goals,Shame,Reach"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I have always said that playing against Allegri\'s sides was difficult because he is a very organised tactician. His players always know what their role is on the field.', '"Difficult,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"Of course, I want to try and overtake the record of goals scored in European cups with the Rossoneri shirt."', '"Goals,Shirt,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', '"When there is a respect, it is much easier to accept the coach\'s decisions."', '"Respect,Accept,Decisions"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd45', 'I have the best job in the world.', '"Best,World,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"Comfort the afflicted, and afflict the comfortable."', '"Comfort,Comfortable,Afflicted"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"Trust everybody, but cut the cards."', '"Trust,Cards,Cut"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'The past always looks better than it was. It\'s only pleasant because it isn\'t here.', '"Time,Past,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"Alcohol is necessary for a man so that he can have a good opinion of himself, undisturbed be the facts."', '"Good,Man,Facts"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"There ain\'t any news in being good. You might write the doings of all the convents of the world on the back of a postage stamp, and have room to spare."', '"Good,World,News"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"A lie with a purpose is one of the worst kind, and the most profitable."', '"Purpose,Lie,Worst"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'An appeal is when you ask one court to show its contempt for another court.', '"Court,Show,Contempt"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'Vice is a creature of such hideous mien... that the more you see it the better you like it.', '"Better,See,More"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'A fanatic is a man that does what he thinks the Lord would do if He knew the facts of the case.', '"Man,Facts,Lord"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'The world is not growing worse and it is not growing better - it is just turning around as usual.', '"World,Better,Worse"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'Most vegetarians look so much like the food they eat that they can be classified as cannibals.', '"Food,Look,Eat"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'The only good husbands stay bachelors: They\'re too considerate to get married.', '"Good,Marriage,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'There are no friends at cards or world politics.', '"Politics,World,No Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', 'Don\'t jump on a man unless he is down.', '"Man,Jump,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"It don\'t make much difference what you study, so long as you don\'t like it."', '"Long,Difference,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd47', '"One of the strangest things about life is that the poor, who need the money the most, are the ones that never have it."', '"Life,Money,Poor"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"We\'re all humans living on this tiny little rock, floating through space at, like, thousands of miles an hour. We should all just get along."', '"Space,Living,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m going to look forward to the future as opposed to looking back at the past.', '"Future,Look,Looking Back"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"You can be a big fish in a small pond, but you\'re only going to be competing against people at that level."', '"Fish,People,Pond"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I really believe in the power of positive thinking and the collective power of people\'s thoughts spawning something into becoming reality.', '"Positive,Power,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I don\'t really pay attention to the news or stuff like that or what\'s going on in politics.', '"Politics,News,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m not going to throw in the towel a moment earlier than I think I have to.', '"Moment,Towel,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'ve always got a couple of tricks up my sleeve.', '"Always,Up,Sleeve"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"It was a big gamble to come to WWE, and it was a big gamble to come to NXT. Honestly, the gamble paid off."', '"Big,Gamble,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When you\'re in NXT, you\'re really fighting and trying to dig down deep and chase your dream."', '"Fighting,Trying,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"How I feel as a person and what I support as a person always remains the same, and that is continuing to support LGBT communities around the world."', '"World,Support,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I can honestly say it was the greatest decision of my life coming to WWE.', '"Life,Decision,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'The \'Demon King\' takes out a lot out of Finn Balor the man emotionally and mentally.', '"King,Man,Out"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I have no intentions of getting in a UFC cage at all!', '"Intentions,Cage,UFC"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I don\'t do well in social environments.', '"Well,Social,Environments"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I do enjoy a level of intensity that I bring when I\'m the Demon, but it\'s a mindset that takes a couple of days to get into; it\'s not something I can do every day."', '"Day,Every Day,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Just the extent of the reach that the WWE Universe has around the world is incredible.', '"World,Universe,Reach"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I try and look at the positives in every situation.', '"Look,Situation,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"It\'s almost like putting on a mask protects you from people\'s judgments and lets you completely flow freely, like, with all your aggression and our animosity against anything."', '"Mask,People,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I came to WWE to be on \'WrestleMania\' and to be in a \'WrestleMania\' main event.', '"WWE,WrestleMania,Event"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'That would be a dream match for me to see Finn Balor versus The Undertaker.', '"Me,See,Match"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When kids tune in and see Jordan Devlin, Trent Seven, Pete Dunne, Wolfgang on the WWE Network, and then they see a poster at the town hall for their local wrestling show, they\'re gonna say, \'Oh my God, that\'s Pete Dunne. I wanna go see him.\'"', '"God,See,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I don\'t see why we should alienate anyone, regardless of sexual orientation, nationality, religion, ethnicity."', '"Religion,See,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'To go from a small wrestling dojo to the Performance Center was just mind-blowing. The sheer scale - I didn\'t think anything like that could possibly exist.', '"Performance,Anything,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I think Finn Balor is more about confidence, a smarter version of Prince Devitt. Otherwise, they have the same core values, same techniques, and the same heart."', '"Heart,Confidence,Values"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"It\'s a very simple answer, how to get my abs so defined. I have a very healthy diet of a lot of laughter. If you laugh all the time, you\'re consistently flexing your abdominals all the time."', '"Time,Diet,Laughter"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'You can only get better by challenging yourself.', '"Yourself,Better,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Going through secondary school in Ireland, everyone\'s like, \'What are you gonna do when you finish school? Go to college? Study business? Study electronics?\' I was like, \'Well I kinda love wrestling, so I don\'t see why I should want to study anything else except wrestling.\' For me, it was a no brainer."', '"Love,Business,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I always wanted to have sort of an alter ego.', '"Ego,Always,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"The dojo system in Japan is something very unique. It prepared me not only for wrestling in the States and around the world, but it also prepared me for how to handle myself as an adult in the real world."', '"Myself,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I was six years old watching wrestling on TV. I was eight years old watching Ultimate Warrior run to the ring at WrestleMania. I was eighteen years old starting out on a journey in the U.K. wanting to be a professional wrestler.', '"Journey,Warrior,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m proud to be the standard-bearer for NXT.', 'Proud', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I think everybody in WWE and NXT want to be involved in WrestleMania. I can huff and puff and push all I want, but that\'s something you just can\'t rush."', '"I Can,Push,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Myself, Karl Anderson, and Luke Gallows are best friends. We travel together, we train together, we eat together, and we do a lot of things together."', '"Best,Travel,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"NXT is its own kind of animal, and you\'re never quite sure how much of that transfers over into WWE and into Monday Night Raw."', '"Night,Animal,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I worry too much about the present to worry about the future.', '"Future,Worry,Present"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I came up in the U.K., which is a very catch-as-catch-can style, and then I somehow ended up in Japan and spent eight years there learning strong style. I got to spend some time in Mexico learning the lucha libre style, and the WWE is a hybrid style of everything mixed together."', '"Time,Learning,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"With regards to the paint, I\'m normally quite introverted and shy. I keep myself to myself, and I find that when I hide behind the paint, so to speak, I\'m able to let myself go more and move more freely than I can without it."', '"Myself,Shy,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Obviously, everyone wants to headline \'WrestleMania.\'"', '"Everyone,Headline,Wants"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'m the sort of person with a very short attention span, and I lose interest in things very quickly."', '"Lose,Person,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I always go back to my days in NXT and look at my feud with Samoa Joe. That was one of the best periods of growth for me.', '"Best,Growth,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'m very lucky to be working at NXT with coaches, especially Matt Bloom, who is open-minded and a great ribber."', '"Great,Bloom,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I can\'t speak of anything but greatness for Roman Reigns. He\'s one of the all-time greats.', '"Greatness,Speak,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"The crowd down in Australia is always so energetic, some of the best crowds in the world to perform in front of."', '"Best,World,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'The Demon character is something I draw on occasion. It\'s something that requires a lot of focus to tap into and really requires the right situation for me to sort of draw on that darker side of my personality.', '"Personality,Focus,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I quite like walking out in my sweet new Balor Club jacket, popping my collar and being Mr. Cool."', '"Cool,Sweet,New"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I started playing soccer when I was 6 years old and started lifting weights when I was 16, so it\'s not like I never exercised."', '"Never,Old,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m a big fan of seeing smaller guys vs. big men.', '"Men,Big,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When I first broke in, I wanted to be the best technical wrestler on the planet."', '"Best,First,Planet"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'m not one for reading comments or reading what people say online because, generally, there\'s a lot of negativity."', '"People,Negativity,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"You can kind of run drills and practice, rehab behind closed doors as much as you can, but there\'s nothing that simulates being in front of a live audience with live TV cameras."', '"Practice,Nothing,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Balor Club is for everyone.', '"Everyone,Club"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When you go out there, and you\'re in the ring, honestly, half the time you forget what city you\'re even in because you\'re so focused on what you\'re doing and the task at hand."', '"Time,City,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'ve been in opening matches of pay-per-views. I\'ve been in main events of pay-per-views, and the same mentality is applied to both, and that is, \'To this point, this is the biggest match of my life, and I\'m gonna go out there and give it everything I have.\'"', '"Life,My Life,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"A lot of people are under the impression that Finn Balor relies on the Demon King, but that is certainly not the case."', '"King,People,Impression"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m very much in a mindset that I take myself out of anything that I\'m not involved in.', '"Myself,Anything,Mindset"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Every child has played video games growing up and played WWE games. To be part of a video game, it\'s an unbelievable experience."', '"Experience,Game,Video Games"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Wrestling has a funny way of regenerating itself, and I\'m sure, in the past, a lot of people have asked questions about \'Who\'s going to replace Sami Zayn in the locker room?\' or \'Who\'s going to replace Kevin Owens in the locker room?\' People always step in."', '"Funny,Step,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I spent two years at NXT and a lot of times questioned, \'When is this going to happen?\' or \'Is this actually going to happen? Am I going to make it to \'Raw?\'\'"', '"Two,Happen,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'ve got a pretty wild imagination, and a lot of times, I have to be reeled back in."', '"Imagination,Back,Wild"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I often find out, once people have trained, you can never really re-train. When you get trained, you learn to lock up; you learn a wrist lock and, okay, onto the next thing, onto the next thing. You never really go back to the fundamentals."', '"People,Back,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I found, going to Japan, working in the dojos, brushing up on the fundamentals, that\'s where I really mastered what I was doing."', '"Doing,Up,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Just remember that when I went to New Japan, nobody knew who I was. And I\'ve done okay."', '"Remember,New,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"As a kid growing up, I was a huge gamer - The NES, SuperNES, N64, GameCube - and I had a GameBoy, which went everywhere with me."', '"Me,Gamer,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Nobody thought Finn Balor would be in the WWE. Here I am.', '"I Am,Nobody,Here"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I heard Samoans have hard heads, but it turns out what Enzo Amore told me about Samoa Joe\'s head was true. His head is S-A-W-F-T."', '"Me,True,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I thrive under pressure.', '"Pressure,Thrive"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Johnny Saint is someone who I studied as a kid.', '"Someone,Who,Kid"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When I came to NXT, it was very much a developmental brand."', '"Brand,Much,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'It wasn\'t until later in my career that I really focused on the importance on making an entrance.', '"Importance,Entrance,Career"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Japan took me in as one of their own and treated me like one of their own.', '"Me,Own,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"If you\'re going to learn about entrances from anyone, you might learn from the Undertaker."', '"About,Going,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I didn\'t realize how much the paint was going to affect how I moved and how I walked. And it wasn\'t something that consciously happened. It was because the first time I\'d done it was a Tokyo Dome show, I want to say in 2013-14, and I walked out there, and I was a completely different person."', '"Time,First Time,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I had to use a lot of the lessons I learned from fighting Samoa Joe and apply them to Bray Wyatt.', '"Fighting,Use,Lessons"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"It\'s been a bit of a struggle getting used to life in the States, adapting to a new lifestyle."', '"Life,Struggle,New"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Hopefully, I can be a good role model for kids, and they can grow up to follow their dreams just like I am."', '"Dreams,Good,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"If you ever have a question or a problem, if you approach Triple H, he might say the most-obvious thing, but it was the last thing you were thinking. As soon as he says it, you\'re thinking, \'Oh my, why didn\'t I think of that?\' He\'s very smart, and we\'re very lucky to have him at our disposal in NXT."', '"Thinking,Smart,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'The NXT women are changing the way women\'s wrestling is viewed. It\'s an inspiration to be able to watch.', '"Women,Way,Inspiration"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"For a long time, we had Raw and SmackDown, and there wasn\'t really anything else. The NXT Universe kinda opened up channels for wrestlers to come in from the independent circuits, like myself."', '"Time,Myself,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"There wasn\'t one defining moment that I said, \'I wanna be a wrestler.\' It was just something that was always inside me."', '"Moment,Me,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"The whole Demon character was designed for people to hate me more and to be scared of me, and it kind of backfired in the sense that people kind of like it now."', '"Character,Hate,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"If I\'m going to draw something, I don\'t know the day before what I\'m going to draw. It\'s just very much an interpretation of how I\'m feeling that day and what I think is the coolest thing in my brain at that very moment."', '"Moment,Brain,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I want to be part of the growth of NXT.', '"Growth,Want,Part"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I spent a lot of time in Japan. To me, I felt like my career was kind of marooned out there. I didn\'t realize the extent of the reach that New Japan had in America and around the world."', '"Time,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I don\'t really like to think too far into the future.', '"Future,Far,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I grew up watching wrestling my whole life, so to get the chance to step in the ring that I\'ve watched on TV so many times is a dream come true."', '"Life,Chance,Step"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'ve seen a lot of different training schools and dojos, and the sheer level of professionalism at the Performance Center and the state-of-the-art facility just knocked me for a six. It really blew me away."', '"Me,Training,Performance"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I\'ve been put into a lot of situations that could be stressful. That\'s really helped me mature, both as a performer and as a man."', '"Man,Me,Mature"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"2010 was an incredible year for me. I won the Best of the Super Juniors, and went on to win the IWGP Junior Heavyweight title. That was an unbelievable achievement."', '"Best,Me,Achievement"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"People won\'t believe this, but I don\'t really like being the center of attention."', '"Believe,People,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"My parents have supported me everywhere I\'ve went: U.K. to Japan, NXT."', '"Me,Parents,Everywhere"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m not a very emotional person.', '"Person,Emotional,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"When I first went to Japan, I was wrestling under my real name. The Japanese people have a great amount of difficulty with the letters f, r and l. So three out of the six letters in my first name they couldn\'t say. It was a bit of a mouthful for those guys."', '"Great,People,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'I\'m normally a really humble guy.', '"Humble,Guy,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I was big into hip-hop as a kid, and when I was eighteen, I got into dance and rave music, which was popular in Ireland at the time."', '"Time,Music,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"Ireland has always been a nation of great athletes from the past: in the nineties, we had Sonia O\'Sullivan and Steve Collins."', '"Great,Past,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"I still can\'t believe I\'m a professional wrestler in the first place. That hasn\'t sunk in yet. I\'m sure I\'ll look back when I\'m 50 or 60, if I make it that far, and think about everything that\'s happened."', '"Look,Believe,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', 'Everyone that watches wrestling as a kid dreams of being a wrestler for WWE.', '"Dreams,Everyone,Watches"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd48', '"My whole career, I\'ve been climbing or chasing or hunting something."', '"Something,Hunting,Chasing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I was never a troublemaker, but I also was never a nerdy kid. I was never a cool kid or a sports kid. At lunchtimes, I never fit in with any cliques, so I\'d end up just walking around the school by myself, listening to music."', '"Cool,Music,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"New York has a deep culture of house and dance music, and to be able to tap into that is my way of shutting off. I go to friends\' parties and local spots around the area: places I can go to, have a dance, and forget about being an actor and the attention."', '"Music,Culture,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"My mum was a child minder, but now she fosters. My dad was in the police force, and now he\'s a private detective."', '"Dad,Police,She"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', 'The power should be in individual democracies in individual communities. It shouldn\'t be an oligarchy or some small group of elite. Power should be with the people and not with some politician or some heir to the throne or some madman.', '"Power,People,Politician"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I will say that Marvel is 100 times more secretive than \'Game of Thrones.\' Like, they\'re not even on the same playing field."', '"Game,Will,More"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I respect Marvel as a company, and I think they\'re great, but never in my life have I looked up to being a superhero."', '"Life,Respect,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I do feel like the media is one of the biggest problems. If you look at all these rolling news channels, they sensationalize the story, they focus on gossip, and they don\'t actually tell the full story."', '"Focus,Look,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I\'ve had this theory for a while, but I think there needs to be a message with the end of \'Game of Thrones.\' You know? I think what needs to happen is ice and fire are going to go to war, a huge war between those two factions, and I think, in that war, they will destroy themselves. There will be complete chaos, complete destruction."', '"War,Fire,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"When I was in drama school, I really got into a dark place. I went to a therapist - it was really helpful to have that dialogue with someone. So I understand anxiety."', '"Drama,School,Dark"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', 'I\'m not a critic. I\'m an actor. I see the role I get given on the page. I try to bring it to life as best as I can.', '"Life,Best,See"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', 'I\'m a huge advocate for human rights and cultural rights. I stand up for minorities and will always continue to do so.', '"Will,Stand,Stand Up"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I find the comic book audience a lot more intense than the fantasy one, definitely."', '"Fantasy,Find,More"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I know feeling pressure gets you nowhere creatively. You\'ve just got to understand the character, understand the story, and just play it to the fullest extent."', '"Character,Pressure,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"At first, I didn\'t know what an actor was. I thought it was an acrobat. I saw acrobats at the circus, and I thought that was interesting. In my head, that was what I imagined I wanted to be when I grew up. Then I realized what an actor was, and I\'ve gravitated to it ever since."', '"Know,Circus,Head"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"For me as an actor, I find it\'s most creative when I\'m bringing myself into the role rather than putting the role on. I feel like it\'s more of a cathartic experience."', '"Experience,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', 'About a year after leaving drama school or a year and a half - and I was working solidly ever since leaving drama school - I picked up \'Game of Thrones.\'', '"Game,Drama,School"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I worked on \'Game Of Thrones\' for six years, so I\'m very well equipped to handle hype surrounding television shows."', '"Game,Television,Hype"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', 'I\'ve always been interested in mindfulness and alternative ways of seeing the world.', '"World,Always,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I get that people want more diversity in TV and film, and I stand by that. I stand in solidarity with better diversity in TV shows, especially for Asian actors. I agree with that 100 per cent."', '"Diversity,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"Women are the strong people in this world, not men. I think TV is finally catching up with that reality, and thank God."', '"God,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"There\'s nothing interesting about seeing our characters for an hour and a half do some flashy flying in the sky and beating up on some buildings. It\'s boring, and people don\'t want that anymore. They want character, and they want story."', '"Sky,Character,Boring"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I\'m a big fan of \'Akira,\' and I think comics are a great place to tell intelligent, fantastical stories. You can say stuff that you wouldn\'t be able to in other mediums."', '"Great,Place,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"I\'ve always been a bit of a lost soul, and I think that goes back to me being adopted and not knowing my roots."', '"Me,Soul,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"A lot of the vibe in London is being sucked dry because of the economic situation. It\'s very expensive, and it gives you nothing back. New York still feels like there\'s stuff going on. People are struggling to create art. There\'s still a vibe."', '"Art,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"\'Thrones\' would be the perfect platform to send a progressive message because right now, our politicians aren\'t telling us any truths. It\'s hard to find a good, meaningful message, so I think it\'s up to storytellers, television shows, and films to have an impact on the world conversation. Is that not what film and television is for?"', '"Good,World,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"Pretty much everyone on my iPod, I\'d like to be friends with. But I\'d say that the main two that I\'d love to get into a conversation with are Werner Herzog and Graham Hancock."', '"Love,Conversation,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd49', '"Every day of my life, I make an effort. Like, everything\'s an effort - a good effort."', '"Life,Good,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"There\'s monsters in all of us, but there\'s also vulnerability."', '"Monsters,Vulnerability,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"So many actors started on soap operas. So yeah, I\'d graduated Julliard and done some theater. I\'ve done a few guest spots on TV but nothing that long-term. I did a little \'E.R.\' back when it was on, and a pilot for \'Cold Case.\'"', '"Nothing,Done,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Soap operas are like boot camps for film actors, so I really learned a lot. It was a masterclass in working for camera. I made myself watch myself every day. I would sort of try and be objective about it and critique myself a little. There\'s a lot more skill set than people realize in soap operas. They shoot, like, 35 scenes a day."', '"Myself,Skill,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Sometimes you\'re watching a great film actor, and if you stand 10 feet away from them, you\'re like, \'God, they\'re terrible. They\'re not doing anything.\' And then you see the close-up, and it\'s so nuanced, and so much expression is happening. They were acting for that camera and for no one else."', '"God,Great,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I started writing when I started acting professionally because, with acting, there\'s so much time when you\'re not working, and there\'s so much rejection and so little you have control of. Writing is something that you can do, and no one can tell you not to."', '"Time,Control,Rejection"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Film and television are so piecemeal. You do one scene, and then you put it to bed, and then you do a scene that comes before. In a play, you have to go from beginning to end every night, and that\'s harder, but also more fulfilling in a way."', '"Night,Beginning,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"A lot of the stuff that\'s happening now, I can trace back to \'Death of a Salesman.\' Francine Maisler, the casting director, saw \'Death of a Salesman\' and called me in for \'Unbroken.\' The casting director of \'Normal Heart\' had seen \'Salesman\' too. I look back on it now, and it\'s like one thing led to another; it was a chain reaction."', '"Death,Heart,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I have been thinking a lot about what we see in villains, how we relate to villains, and what it is about certain villains that we actually empathize with. Like Macbeth. We\'re not supposed to like a guy who kills the king and takes over, but there\'s something about him we\'re really fascinated by."', '"King,Thinking,See"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', 'I want to keep pushing my boundaries. One of the biggest things I learned from \'Unbroken\' is that you can go a lot further than you think you can. We often underestimate our actual capabilities.', '"Underestimate,Go,Boundaries"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Ryan Murphy, he basically tries to find something that\'s a pulse, a pressure point in our culture, and he grabs it, and he squeezes it. I think \'Freak Show\' has a lot to do with the entertainment industry and the way we entertain ourselves: the objectification of people and the lengths we\'ll go for our own amusement."', '"Culture,Way,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', 'I caught the acting bug from my dad.', '"Dad,Acting,Bug"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I found L.A. much less responsive to the name Juilliard than New York was. In New York, that name actually means something. People will look up from their desks when you walk in. In L.A. it\'s, \'Oh yeah, that\'s a music school. What do you play?\'"', '"Music,Walk,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"In film, you\'re so much in the hands and at the mercy of the editor, so sometimes it\'s good to watch it just to see how it turns out - it can be so different than how you imagined it. But sometimes it\'s better to just let it go for your own sense of self worth."', '"Good,Better,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', 'That\'s one of my real goals is to keep theater in my life.', '"Life,Goals,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"At first, before you meet her, you\'re like, \'I\'m gonna meet Angelina Jolie! I\'m talking to Angelina Jolie!\' And then, within a matter of five minutes, you\'re like, \'Oh, I\'m just talking to my director,\' and it\'s just back to work. She really is all about the work. She\'s so surprisingly down-to-earth."', '"Work,Back,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Writing is something I\'ve always done on the side. I thought that no one would be interested, so I kept it to myself."', '"Myself,Done,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I was playing a defensive guard in \'My All American\' who is a really fast runner, so a lot of my training was running. I wasn\'t too worried about bulking up because he was supposed to be on the small side."', '"Training,Fast,American"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I played baseball growing up, second base, and then when I got to high school,it just didn\'t exist there."', '"Baseball,High,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I think in some ways, acting and writing are the same. You\'re getting inside the skin of someone else; you\'re creating their language and their actions. As a writer, you have to see the whole picture and the structure, and you have to understand every character."', '"Character,Skin,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', 'I would love to do Shakespeare in New York.', '"Love,New,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I would love to play Henry IV, Henry V, and Hamlet."', '"Love,Play,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', 'I\'ve learned 90 percent of what I know from watching and listening to actors. A good leading actor is the rock of the show. Their energy and their tone really sets the groundwork for how everything is going to work. I\'ve been lucky to deal with stars who are very giving and generous.', '"Work,Good,Stars"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"Doing theater anywhere, especially in L.A., is a constant uphill battle, and there\'s also the unsexy parts of the business that you\'re faced with, like getting money. It\'s a really great thing to do. You feel like you\'re really an artist when you\'re doing that and you\'re in a company of artists."', '"Business,Money,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I\'m usually late to the game on shows and watch them after they\'ve aired. But I love \'House of Cards,\' \'The Killing,\' \'Orange Is the New Black,\' loved \'True Detective,\' and \'Arrested Development\' when it was on. Also \'The Wire,\' though I was way late to the game on that."', '"Love,Black,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I\'m a klutz, through and through."', 'Through', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4a', '"I went to an Arts High School, so everyone there was kind of anti-clique, though they still happened. I guess I was in the theatre-dork clique. Not to be confused with the musical-theatre-dork clique."', '"School,Confused,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Life gets weird enough without having to worry about whether you are covered for this or have to have a deductible for that, so the less stress when you are in need, the better."', '"Life,Better,Stress"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I love retro culture. I love retro games; I love retro music.', '"Love,Music,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I think if I\'m with a friend group, I try to be as funny as possible, and I don\'t always succeed, obviously."', '"Funny,Always,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I mean if anyone\'s comfortable being famous, they\'re a psychopath."', '"Famous,Comfortable,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'m good at reading people. If I wasn\'t an actor, I would be a psychologist."', '"Good,People,Reading"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Sewer rats are really gross.', '"Sewer,Really,Rats"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'People deal with death differently; some even laugh at funerals.', '"Death,People,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I don\'t want to be mean to people. I try to be as nice as possible to everyone.', '"People,Possible,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Messing up lines is always embarrassing for me.', '"Me,Always,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'My whole thing is having the perfect balance. Let\'s say I go to school. I have a day at school. That\'s the perfect amount of reality. Then I go and play music with my band. Then I go home and hang out with my family and my pets. I think that\'s the perfect amount of reality time.', '"Family,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I do ride my bike a lot.', '"Ride,Bike,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My parents were in high school and college in the \'80s, so let\'s just say I\'ve heard some stuff, man. We listen to a lot of music and watch lots of great films, but the real context they provide from that era is about politics."', '"Politics,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I wanted to do something in film. I wanted to make my own movies. Something clicked in my brain, like, \'Oh, I can physically act! I can go on open casting calls and audition for something.\'"', '"Movies,Brain,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'The Goonies\' I love. \'Heathers\' too.', '"Love,Too,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I don\'t want to get typecast and I\'ve been doing a lot of stuff to make that happen and not be the case.', '"Doing,Want,Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My dad is a screenwriter, so he always used to watch movies for inspiration when I was a baby. I would watch movies with him, I guess, in the background."', '"Movies,Dad,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I read \'Carrie\' when I was younger and that\'s one of my favourite books.', '"Younger,Books,Read"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I wanted to be a director and comedian and my plan was to go to NYU. I wanted to be in UCB.', '"Go,Plan,Director"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Most of the fans of Calpurnia are \'Stranger Things\' fans, which is not a big deal at all. They\'re super loyal and incredible, and really do like the music. It\'s the people who aren\'t fans of the music and are just there because of \'Stranger Things\' that really bother me."', '"Music,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Jonah Hill is super cool.', '"Cool,Hill,Super"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Meeting Ryan Reynolds was really cool, and Blake Lively."', '"Cool,Lively,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'d love to make a horror movie, that\'s definitely where I want to be one day."', '"Love,Day,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Well, I kind of did the math in my head when I was like, 9. I was like, \'Well, if I want to make films\' - because I want to be a director - \'I could just go on a film set and learn there.\' And then I ended up falling in love with acting and the set and making friends all the time. And so I\'ve just been doing that ever since."', '"Love,Time,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"It\'s my given, full name. Finn\'s not short for anything; it\'s just Finn Wolfhard. And then Wolfhard means, I think, heart of the wolf in German."', '"Heart,Name,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"The biggest thing for me, I hate going to concerts where no-one\'s moving. Everyone should be dancing and having a good time."', '"Time,Good,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'There\'s so many influential albums my parents would put on. Like the first album I ever heard was \'Help!\' by the Beatles and from there I just loved rock music.', '"Music,Parents,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Okay, I like the Clash. I like Tears for Fears. I like A-ha."', '"Tears,Okay,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"During \'Stranger Things 3,\' I shot \'It: Chapter Two,\' so I would shoot on my days off, which was super tiring and stressful, but really rewarding at the same time. Basically, I shot \'It: Chapter Two\' and \'Stranger Things 3\' at the same time."', '"Time,Stranger,Shoot"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"If I lounge around for too long, I get really bored. I have to be doing something."', '"Long,Doing,Bored"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I probably saw \'Jaws\' when I was 10.', '"Saw,Jaws"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"It\'s really cool when the thing you are working on as a small team gets embraced by millions, but in the end, it\'s about your character and the script and your director and the rest of the cast and crew."', '"Cool,Character,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Yeah, ever since I was super-young I had a lot of dreams - I wanted to be a musician, I wanted to be a skateboarder."', '"Dreams,Had,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"It\'s intriguing to me, when I see a horror script, or something like that, that\'s actually original. I think that\'s why I love \'Stranger Things,\' because it\'s not just horror, it\'s everything, and when they use horror it\'s right."', '"Love,Me,Stranger"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Obviously \'Stranger Things\' has given me the launching pad to have creative license for whatever I want, and I love doing the show, but when it comes to music, I want to distance myself as much as possible."', '"Love,Music,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"For me, I need to listen to music in the morning, and after, it\'s kind of like a shower, you know what I mean? It\'s kind of getting rid of everything. I always play music after I act. It\'s not a conscious thing, like, \'Oh finally, I need to do this,\' it\'s kind of a constant need."', '"Morning,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"One time, when I was really young, my dad and brother were watching \'Team America,\' the Trey Parker and Matt Stone movie. I walked in and they didn\'t know I was there, but I got really freaked out by the marionettes - just the look of them, their mouths, those grins. That cemented in my brain."', '"Time,Dad,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I mainly use Twitter, Instagram and Snapchat. Those are my three."', '"Three,Use,Twitter"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Well, we shoot for so long on \'Stranger Things\' that I know Atlanta really well."', '"Long,Stranger,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I have lots of friends who are musicians and it is such a huge victory to survive in music, period - but if you get sick or injured and don\'t have the kind of coverage we get in Canada, you are doomed."', '"Music,Victory,Canada"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Like, everyone knows that we all need health care, but not only is it insanely expensive for most people in America, there are so many self-employed people who really struggle when faced with injury and disability and illness."', '"Health,Struggle,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'d recommend anyone watch \'Harold and Maude,\' \'cause it helps a lot with fear of death."', '"Death,Fear,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I love being Canadian.', '"Love,Canadian,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"It\'s going to sound cheesy, but if I have family and friends I don\'t really care where I am."', '"Family,I Am,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Honestly, if acting never worked out, I would have done music."', '"Music,Done,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I never liked horror up until I was like 10 years old.', '"Never,Old,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I think I\'m really bad at voice acting.', '"Bad,Voice,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Everyone wants to be funny. Maybe not everyone, but to an extent."', '"Funny,Everyone,Maybe"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"If I hadn\'t done the PUP video, I probably wouldn\'t be playing music right now."', '"Music,Done,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'PUP introduced me to so much more amazing music. They really shaped my sound.', '"Music,Amazing,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'d seen all of John Hughes\'s movies. All the Spielberg stuff. A bunch of \'80s horror, like \'Evil Dead.\'"', '"Movies,Dead,Evil"', '2023-05-29 11:44:00', '2023-05-29 11:44:00'),
	('392511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'It was cool when the Duffers assigned a list of movies to watch.', '"Cool,Movies,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"If you don\'t realize that there are great rock bands out there, you should look for them."', '"Great,Look,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Pup, who\'s like the most amazing, they\'re keeping rock \'n\' roll and punk alive."', '"Amazing,Alive,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I guess with a Netflix show, if you\'re a kid, it\'s all dependent on how you\'re raised and if you have access to it."', '"Netflix,Guess,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I usually just watch YouTube videos or reruns on Netflix of older TV shows like \'Family Guy\' and stuff. But I still really want to start watching more TV.', '"Family,YouTube,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I watch a lot of YouTube videos. I like game play channels like the Game Grumps. But I mostly watch sketch comedy.', '"Game,YouTube,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I really used to like TVMaxwell, which is a classic, amazing, super-underrated comedy channel. And Cyndago was great."', '"Great,Amazing,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I\'m always interested in horror and the supernatural.', '"Always,Supernatural,Horror"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I love \'80s and \'90s music.', '"Love,Music,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I love Nirvana, Joy Division, and New Order - older alternative, I guess."', '"Love,Joy,New"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Scary movies, for me, I used to be insanely scared of."', '"Movies,Me,Scared"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I think growing up in Vancouver is a different lifestyle than growing up in most other places.', '"Lifestyle,Growing Up,Places"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'d actually love to do more comedy, but what I really wanna do is an indie drama - an intense indie road-trip movie."', '"Love,Drama,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I\'m definitely not eager to grow up, but I do like some adult stuff."', '"Grow,Adult,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'The Duffers like that; they like watching their characters grow.', '"Grow,Watching,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I need time to do whatever I want to do. What happens to an actor that has no life experience? They don\'t know how to act as a different role. So, that\'s really important to do."', '"Life,Experience,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My parents are great. On every job, my whole family and I try to get as many breaks as I can."', '"Family,Great,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Jason Reitman is an amazing director; he\'s really amazing with his actors and crew.', '"Amazing,Crew,He"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"When I was younger, I acted in some Shakespeare stuff; I did one Shakespeare camp."', '"Younger,Did,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Doing a scene by yourself is scarier - you know you don\'t have other people to fall back on.', '"Yourself,People,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'The movies I was scared by at three or four are now some of my favorite movies of all time.', '"Time,Movies,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I\'ve really never discovered a band from Spotify or anything. I\'ve really only discovered it from friends.', '"Never,Anything,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"There\'s a band from Brooklyn called Frankie Cosmos, which is very nice."', '"Cosmos,Nice,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I\'m not a big radio listener.', '"Big,Radio,Listener"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I love doing both animation and live acting.', '"Love,Live,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"To see a hacker actually hacking is not the most interesting thing visually, and it\'s pretty boring as an actor: a hacker taps on her keyboard. There\'s really not much more than that."', '"Boring,Hacking,Hacker"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'Weird Al\' is awesome and so humble.', '"Humble,Weird,Awesome"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'We need musicians! We need them healthy - we need to dance and we need to escape - and none of that is possible when musicians themselves need support.', '"Support,Escape,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Any chance I get to see a band that I like, I take it."', '"Chance,See,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'One day I\'m going to open up a club or a concert venue where it\'s all ages and really fun. That\'d be awesome.', '"Fun,Day,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'The aliens from \'Attack the Block\' - I thought they were some of the most unique and creative movie monsters I had ever seen. From the jet-black hair to the neon blue teeth.', '"Blue,Hair,Unique"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I try to keep my voice natural for each character, but the spirit and the cadence and breathing for each character is totally different. It\'s those things that set each role apart from the others."', '"Character,Voice,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I really would not be where I am today if I hadn\'t done those PUP videos. It just showed me so much. It taught me so much about music and acting and being your own boss.', '"Music,Today,Boss"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I don\'t take the Internet and social media very seriously. I\'ve grown up around social media but to me what happens on the Internet just doesn\'t feel real.', '"Me,Social Media,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I never knew anyone who have growing up who had a clown at their birthday party. They are something I think of as being from the past. So I never had strong feelings about them. I do think that they can be creepy, I guess it depends on the clown."', '"Birthday,Past,Feelings"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I\'ve been asked to school dances.', '"School,Been,Dances"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I learn a new thing every single day about acting, about directing, about producing."', '"Day,New,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"The more I read scripts, the more I learn about scripts, basically."', '"More,About,Basically"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My dad, who is a screenwriter, showed me all these great movies. He showed me \'E.T.\' when I was 2-years-old, and I just kind of progressed from there. It was also my brother. We\'d always watch movies together, and he\'d do these voices and he\'d always want to do skits and he\'d come up with stuff with me."', '"Great,Movies,Dad"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I love learning on set, it\'s the best acting school ever."', '"Love,Best,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I love acting, of course, and I would still love to keep acting, but I want to try my hands at so many things."', '"Love,Hands,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"The things I want to focus on are music, writing, directing, and developing stuff."', '"Music,Focus,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My favorite thing is to have collectives. Even when it comes to filmmaking as well, filmmaking and music and most art in general, I feel like everyone should have the same say. If you\'re in a collective, I feel like everyone should have the same say."', '"Art,Music,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"My dad would play \'The Blue Album\' a lot, the first Weezer album, and that influenced my alternative indie thing and that\'s kind of how I found tons and most of my favorite bands."', '"Dad,Blue,First"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I definitely do have a persona onstage. I definitely am a completely different person, but I\'m still having a lot of fun and there\'s a lot of acting that goes into it. But I haven\'t been playing many shows when I\'m working on acting as much because it\'s tiring, number one. And number two, it\'s hard for your mind to makeup what it wants to do."', '"Mind,Fun,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', 'I was raised in a household where kids\' opinions were just as valued as adults and I think that was important for me.', '"Me,Important,Opinions"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"Some bands I\'m obsessed with but I get sick of listening to their music after a while, but that hasn\'t happened with Twin Peaks."', '"Music,Listening,Sick"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"I get recognized on the street and stuff, which is cool but it\'s also weird."', '"Cool,Street,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4b', '"There\'s always something really bad that happens in \'Stranger Things,\' I think the more fun we\'re having at the beginning, the higher the drop."', '"Fun,Bad,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I think if you\'re not trying to change things a little bit, you\'re not evolving."', '"Change,Trying,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I feel like you\'re able to be your most creative in private environments, and not a studio where an A&R person is coming in, telling us a song isn\'t a smash."', '"Song,Feel,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"You go to a truck stop and there are key chains with names on them, and there\'s no Finneas. There\'s no Billie. They\'re little things, but as a kid, you just feel weirdly ostracized."', '"Feel,Little Things,Chains"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"To me, my favorite joke on a stand-up special is when someone says something and you go, \'Oh my God, I\'ve been thinking that my whole life, I\'ve just never said it to anyone else.\' Those little kinda quiet, personal observations you make that nobody else has talked about yet."', '"Life,God,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I was on a TV show called \'Glee.\' I mean, I was on the real tail end of that show; it was already way past its peak. But still, for me aged 17 landing something like that was a big deal."', '"Me,Past,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'Love has always been the most important thing to me and the thing by which my life is guided.', '"Life,Love,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I really value just being able to go out and grab a coffee or going to a movie and not have anyone recognize me.', '"Me,Value,Coffee"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'The music that I listened to when I was growing up was the most important to me forever.', '"Music,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'We wrote and recorded the \'Bond\' song on a tour bus in Texas.', '"Bond,Song,Bus"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I don\'t particularly like recording studios, they tend to be lifeless and without any natural light, so I wanted to record wherever we lived. We just don\'t want to be bound to a studio to who we\'d have to pay untold sums to."', '"Light,Recording,Wherever"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"People were like, \'he\'s collaborating with Taylor Swift\' and I was like, \'I am?\' I think she\'s wonderful. Her songwriting has inspired me for years."', '"Me,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I stopped telling people what lyrics meant to them when I saw them tattoo it on them, because it clearly meant much more to them than it ever did to me."', '"Me,People,More"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'All my favorite songs ever are love songs. Probably topped by \'The Luckiest\' by Ben Folds.', '"Love,Love Songs,Luckiest"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"The excuse of having a dog is great, because before I had a dog, I wouldn\'t be like, \'I need to go hike for two hours\'; my girlfriend would have been like, \'What are you doing?\' Now I take the dog, and she comes with me."', '"Great,Me,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I think in modern communication studies, we put a lot of emphasis on our relationships and our family relationships. Our relationships with our parents, and our siblings. I felt that there was this gap in content about communication with people who are super close to you in your peer group."', '"Family,Communication,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"In my perfect world, I get to be a professional musician and still go to Trader Joe\'s."', '"World,Perfect,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Production has always been a fantasy of mine, and I got really lucky and had a sister who put a lot of faith and trust in me, and was very collaborative, and was willing to let me produce her entire album."', '"Faith,Trust,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"The amount of times I\'ve been told something by artists I\'m working with, which I\'m sure they haven\'t told even their significant other or families, is shocking."', '"Something,Even,Shocking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I\'m just obsessed with music I guess.', '"Music,Guess,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'It\'s always important to be checking in with people you love.', '"Love,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'When we are making a song for Billie I want it to resonate and speak the truth with her and want it to be a piece of fabric she can wear.', '"Truth,Song,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I don\'t think if you set out to make an album to get a bunch of Grammy nominations... you just have to set out to make an album you\'ll really love.', '"Love,Think,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Even though we\'re all together making songs and I produce them, it\'s so her vision. Especially when we walk out on stage every night. It\'s so meticulously thought through by Billie and I admire that endlessly in her."', '"Walk,Vision,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"What I really didn\'t want to do is work with other people and have them go, \'Oh, Finneas just does that sound for everybody.\' The Billie sound is only Billie - I\'ll only do that for her."', '"Work,People,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I don\'t analyze songs because I think it will make me a better songwriter, I just do it out of sheer curiosity."', '"Me,Curiosity,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I\'m a big believer in the benefit of a home studio. You\'re sitting there and maybe you don\'t know the next line. So you go outside for a second, maybe. Make a sandwich. Play with the dog. Or watch an episode of \'The Office,\' whatever. And then it clicks, you run back into the room, and you\'ve got it. It\'s not like your creativity is on the clock."', '"Home,Creativity,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"To be honest, I\'ve found so many more friends in the music industry than people I disagree with. I certainly haven\'t been made to feel like an outsider."', '"Music,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"You might think of Hollywood as this full-on glamorous thing and to us it was like, \'All right, mom\'s got an audition. Do you want to sit in traffic for 50 minutes and go in with her?\'"', '"Mom,Glamorous,Traffic"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I never get tired of writing about love.', '"Love,Tired,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Working on TV shows was fun, but I felt crazy pressured and stressed."', '"Fun,Crazy,Felt"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"When I started, I felt that there was this incredible amount of doubt of my ability as a producer."', '"Doubt,Ability,Incredible"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Definitely for me and my sister, wherever we are the most comfortable is where the best music\'s going to be made."', '"Best,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I don\'t really have any interest in recording at places that are institutionalized for recording.', '"Recording,Interest,Places"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I\'m not a control freak in that like I boss everybody around, but like a control freak and like, I like knowing exactly what I get to do that day and having a say."', '"Boss,Day,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'All the albums that I grew up listening to were produced by one person.', '"Listening,Person,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I think the whole response to our art being so positive is that it rings true and it feels a unique thing and I feel that was the thing that we strive for in the beginning was to not conform to any preconceived notions of what we should be doing.', '"Positive,Art,True"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I felt really lucky in that I\'ve gotten to know some of my favorite artists; I get to tell them how important they are to me. But that doesn\'t always make me want to work with people. I feel like if I\'m going to work with somebody, it\'s because I feel like I actually have something to add to them."', '"Work,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I really always wanted to be an adult. I didn\'t really like being an adolescent at all.', '"Always,Adult,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I am not a very superstitious person, but I do believe in mental preparation."', '"Believe,I Am,Preparation"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"So, I\'ll walk around with - just an iPhone will work - but sometimes I\'ll bring, like, a little mobile recorder and I\'ll just, like, if hear an interesting sound, I\'ll just record it. And then later, I\'ll listen through them and I\'ll go like, \'I wonder how can I use that?\'"', '"Work,Walk,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"In the alternate reality where I wasn\'t involved at all, and I\'d been like, just, sweating my way through, trying to have a music career for years? And then my sibling had one and I wasn\'t involved at all? I think I\'d be very tortured by it. But the fact that we\'ve had one in tandem makes a lot of sense."', '"Music,Reality,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"You know, I grew up very self-taught."', '"Know,Up,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I have always loved Ben Folds, he\'s like an idol of mine, a hero of mine."', '"Hero,Always,Mine"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Imagine if somebody was like, \'Who\'s the next Timothee Chalamet?\' It\'s like, he\'s currently Timothee Chalamet."', '"Next,Imagine,He"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'There\'s always a better word than a swear word.', '"Better,Always,Swear"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"When I wrote \'When the Party\'s Over,\' it had a universal quality."', '"Quality,Universal,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I mainly try to foster long-term collaborative relationships.', '"Try,Long-Term,Relationships"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'Kids have tools to do what I\'m doing.', '"Doing,Tools,Kids"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I try not to shy away from specificity.', '"Shy,Try,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I always wanted to be on tour or making albums.', '"Always,Wanted,Making"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Being able to hear an artist and emulate them has been a huge part of being successful as a producer and co-writer. I think it\'s a problem when a producer comes in to work with an artist, and you can\'t hear the artist as well anymore. It\'s very important to me to be invisible."', '"Work,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Everything sounds better when Billie sings it, so the only ones I\'ll keep for myself are ones that really feel just super personal to me in their content, like this is my life story and maybe not anybody else\'s."', '"Life,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I think that\'s probably the number one reason why collaboration is good. You disagree with each other about things and then what we always say is whichever one of us is more passionate about the issue is the winner because if you care about something enough to fight for it, that means it\'s probably a good thing."', '"Good,Fight,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If I\'m writing with or for someone else, it just has to feel true and real for them. It has to feel like they\'re being honest. If it\'s for myself, it\'s the same thing. It has to be something I can mean when I say it."', '"Myself,True,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I love pop songs so much and I don\'t put a ton of pressure on myself as a solo artist to always write the most commercial feeling thing, I just want to write things I would love to listen to."', '"Love,Myself,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"A lot of the time, in pop music especially, there\'s reverb. And the reason is that reverb makes vocals sound better 99% of the time. It makes the notes ring out."', '"Time,Music,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I have nothing against reverb.', '"Nothing,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I think we\'re always looking for ways to inject a sense of humor into our music.', '"Humor,Music,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If I\'m making a song with Billie, then it\'s for Billie... She has to want to wear that song every day. And I think I try to do the same thing when I\'m making a song for myself... I try to treat them both that way, like I\'m sort of A&R-ing her and then A&R-ing myself."', '"Myself,Day,Treat"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'Obviously I\'m very grateful \'Bad Guy\' is doing so well - it\'s shocking and surprising and gratifying - but I do think it\'s important to try to make the next song that people are gonna be excited about.', '"Grateful,Song,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'It\'s important to recognize when a song remains important to you.', '"Song,Important,Recognize"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Usually, I get bored of my stuff almost immediately."', '"Bored,Get,Almost"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"We were a very crunchy, sort of hippie-dippy family."', '"Family,Very,Sort"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Billie doesn\'t actually like recording sessions at all. We like making music together. She doesn\'t like going to some big studio and having them pretend to be a therapist for a couple hours. So by default, we always make the good stuff together."', '"Good,Music,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Our mom cooks well, and we cook poorly. We try."', '"Mom,Try,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I\'m not very interested in fame or notoriety at all - in fact, I\'d be pretty bummed out if I woke up one day and I was, like, super, super famous. But the flipside of that is that I\'m really passionate about my music, I\'m really proud of it and I want it to be heard by as many people as possible, and I\'m willing to embrace whatever comes with that."', '"Music,Famous,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"As soon as you make anything that people like, you get all these new artists hitting you up like \'I want to sound just like Billie Eilish.\' And I\'m always like, \'Absolutely not.\'"', '"New,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"The way that we tried to approach every piece of music is, if the song had a brain, it would be aware of its catalog."', '"Music,Brain,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I am just fascinated by music and I want to know how to identify all the things I love about it; to me music theory is like learning another language and then being able to explain how much you love something more clearly.', '"Love,Learning,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If you\'re thinking about all the possibilities of your life, there are extreme negatives, which you hope don\'t happen, and extreme positives, which you just aren\'t willing to think about because you think you\'ll jinx it."', '"Life,Hope,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'People don\'t come to see a Billie Eilish show to come to see me. They come to see her. So I just try not to screw up too much on my instruments.', '"Me,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I\'ve learned a lot from my mom and my dad. I learn a lot every time I watch Billie perform.', '"Time,Mom,Dad"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If you can use songs as a tool, vehicle for empathy and a deeper understanding of how people are feeling and how people\'s emotions work, there\'s a lot of good that can come from that."', '"Work,Good,Empathy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Well, I mean there are so many producers that inspire me. I used to try to imitate production by certain people. And now I\'m only interested in doing the opposite of that. I\'m only interested in doing production that like no one\'s ever done before."', '"Me,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I feel like the thing that I\'ve learned a lot is when you\'re involved in something, you don\'t always get to appreciate it for what it is as much. You\'re focused on the details and how you can make it better. It\'s kind of torture."', '"Better,Feel,Details"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"You know, that\'s kind of always been our philosophy: not letting the place that we are get in the way of making great music."', '"Music,Great,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"To me, as a producer, I always want something to set stuff apart."', '"Me,Always,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I idolize my kid sister, so I get it. I understand why other people do too."', '"People,Why,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"My dreams as a kid were so far below the Grammys, like, maybe selling out a show, or, like, seeing your album on a shelf in an Urban Outfitters... and the Grammys are so far above that. It\'s very ridiculous."', '"Dreams,Seeing,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I usually don\'t like to annoy people in asking to work with them.', '"Work,People,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If you need to record live instruments, especially drums, it\'s still best to do it in a studio."', '"Best,Live,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'Everybody has different taste and everyone\'s favourite song is different and that\'s great.', '"Great,Song,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I remember, one time, my dad took me and Billie to a fair. I was probably 7 years old, Billie must have been 3, and she put footie pyjamas on and then put a second pair of underwear on over the pyjamas. I remember being like, \'What is Billie wearing?!\' and my dad was like, \'She\'s happy with it. Let\'s go!\'"', '"Time,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I think that, for us, the thing that no one can take away from you is that if you make something that they\'ve never heard before, they\'re gonna respond to that. They may not love it, it may not be their favourite thing, but no one can take different from you."', '"Love,Never,Respond"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"Well, predominately, if I\'m writing for another artist, I\'m sitting there with them and we\'re writing it together."', '"Together,Sitting,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I feel like a lot of music producers have, like, the same toolbox. And I think, like, to me, as a producer, like, I want something to set my stuff apart."', '"Music,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I just have no interest in being at a party.', '"Interest,Just,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'There\'s no other person I like working with as much as my sister.', '"Person,Sister,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I love Griffith Park.', '"Love,Park,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I think it\'s really easy to be the altruistic hero of your own narrative and story.', '"Hero,Easy,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I find that when I\'m in an argument and I\'m angry, I can\'t even form a sentence well. You say something and then later you\'re like \'That\'s not even what I meant at all!\'"', '"Angry,Argument,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"For me, I\'m going to try to make my favorite song over the most popular song."', '"Me,Song,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I came to NAMM once and saw this guitar that self-tuned, and I thought, \'Wow, this is the future!\' And I\'ve never seen it again."', '"Future,Guitar,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'I\'m a bad guitar tuner. I have to pay somebody to tune my guitars.', '"Guitar,Bad,Pay"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If you\'re paying attention and you\'ve been a good listener, you learn every day."', '"Good,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', 'My feeling is that everybody starts out as an emulator. You follow their approach and that\'s how learning works. The pivot is that I don\'t think you\'re going to break new ground unless you do something different.', '"Learning,New,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I had a very positive, wonderful, happy upbringing, and still, for several reasons, I really didn\'t enjoy being a child very much. I felt that I had no control over my life and everything seemed scarier and larger than life."', '"Positive,Life,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"I\'m not an author, but as a songwriter, I\'m afforded this kind of luxurious ambiguity in songs of being able to confess the secrets of my relationships with people and face basically no consequences, or ask for no approval or permission."', '"Face,People,Secrets"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"If I have experienced something in my life, it\'s probably going to be written about, and I don\'t particularly care if the person I\'m writing about wants to be written about."', '"Life,My Life,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4c', '"The first time I ever heard Airborne Toxic Event, my friend was turning 11 or something. And he had a paintball birthday party where him and me and two of our other friends went out to these paintball courses and I got obliterated. I don\'t think I got one hit."', '"Birthday,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I spent most of my teenage years in the National Theatre.', '"Theatre,National,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"I don\'t aspire to have her career, or to be as talented as her, because I\'d feel like I was shooting myself down in flames. If you have a parent who is that successful and set them as a benchmark, then everything is going to be disappointing."', '"Myself,Feel,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'It\'s an amazingly daunting prospect to play any part you\'ve seen someone else play brilliantly.', '"Someone,Play,Seen"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"I actually wanted to be a dancer, though I doubt anyone now would pay to see me in a leotard!"', '"Me,Doubt,See"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I think Ma is more honest than I am sometimes.', '"I Am,Sometimes,More"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I want to play Miss Adelaide in \'Guys and Dolls.\' Really badly.', '"Want,Play,Miss"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"Ma did a play called \'Entertaining Strangers\' when I was about 14, which totally changed my life, I loved it so much."', '"Life,My Life,Strangers"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I\'ve worked with a couple of people in my career that have stopped me dead in my tracks because they make it look so effortless and so extraordinary. One of them is Ben Daniels and the other is Chris Larkin.', '"Look,Me,Dead"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I\'d love to do a play with Ma but I don\'t know whether that\'s like literally filling in your own grave and putting the gravestone on top.', '"Love,Know,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"I just take work a day at a time and hope that people believe in you and your ability, even if you don\'t quite believe in it yourself."', '"Work,Hope,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I don\'t spend as much time with my mother as I would love to because she is always working.', '"Love,Time,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I don\'t drink any more so I switched my obsession to musicals.', '"Drink,More,Obsession"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'Some jobs you take because they are good for the heart.', '"Good,Heart,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"My mother would strike me off if I didn\'t say theatre was incredibly important, and when you see something like \'Network\' at the National Theatre, my god it\'s important. You feel like you can\'t breathe."', '"God,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I happen to think Ruth Wilson is jaw-droppingly brilliant.', '"Brilliant,Think,Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"I\'m me, and I\'ve got the cards that I\'ve been dealt."', '"Me,Cards,Dealt"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I love being surrounded by my family at weekends.', '"Love,Family,Surrounded"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I can\'t think of many places I\'d rather spend Saturday afternoon than in a tattoo parlor.', '"Afternoon,Places,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I adore tattoos. They\'re not painful; you just get an urge to swear a lot.', '"Just,Get,Tattoos"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'Saturday afternoon I\'ll go shopping. Always. I can find things to buy wherever I am.', '"I Am,Shopping,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'My father was my mother\'s greatest flag waver.', '"Father,Flag,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I was 18 and had an inverted light bulb moment where I thought that nothing I could do or say or how I looked was ever going to be good enough.', '"Good,Moment,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'The way I got through thinking that I was very boring and very unsparkly was by being the first person in the bar and being the person that bought the drinks for everyone.', '"Thinking,Boring,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'My mother very bravely put me into rehab two weeks after my father died.', '"Me,Father,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I\'ve got a terrible crush on someone and last week mum was coaching me - it was a real masterclass - on how to very casually say hello to him. I had to talk to her hand. Tears were pouring down our faces.', '"Me,Tears,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'Who wouldn\'t want to work with someone you so utterly respect and you\'re such good friends with?', '"Work,Respect,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'Dad was much more critical. I did a comedy in Windsor and he came round afterwards with a load of paperwork and said nothing about my performance - just: \'I\'ve got some forms for you to sign.\'', '"Dad,Nothing,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I had one critic who wrote: \'Finty Williams is like her mother in looks if not in talent.\' It\'ll be on my gravestone.', '"Talent,Mother,Looks"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"There are a lot of people who are very willing to put my mother on a pedestal, which is a lonely existence. She wants to dispute that so much that she will literally do anything for anybody."', '"People,Will,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"It\'s a knack that my mother doesn\'t have. The only audiobook she ever did she had to leave after the first day, because she couldn\'t string two sentences together. It\'s about the only thing she can\'t do."', '"Together,Day,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'Ironically at drama school I was told I didn\'t have a voice conducive for radio.', '"Drama,School,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"I don\'t know whether, if your father is a brain surgeon, people go, \'He\'s not as good a brain surgeon as his father.\' I don\'t know whether that happens, but because of who Ma is, a lot of people have an opinion, which they form before they get to know me or before they see what I can do."', '"Good,Brain,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', 'I don\'t know under what lighting I can play Juliet. Maybe with a small night light illuminating the stage.', '"Night,Light,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4d', '"If she wasn\'t my mother, I\'d want her to be my best friend."', '"Best,Mother,She"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"My whole life, people have been saying, Why are you so angry?"', '"Life,Anger,Angry"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'There aren\'t many poster children for cool angst. Everybody thinks it\'s cool if you\'re the bad girl.', '"Cool,Children,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'Nothing that you do will ever feel good if you let people convince you that you have no choice.', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Life is all about the friendship and the love and the music. It sounds silly, but it is. I want to have that experience as much as I can as an adult, not as a kid doing something that people are telling her she has to do. If anyone gets in my way, I\'m going to get them out of my way."', '"Life,Friendship,Love"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I still don\'t know what Episcopalian means.', '"Know,Still,Means"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Rape is the most humiliating thing that can be done to you; it\'s the most vulnerable that you can be. But once I realized that, I became a stronger person and faced all my fears."', '"Done,Stronger,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I never thought I\'d be in a position where people would be talking about my sexuality and saying how good I look in underwear.', '"Good,Look,Sexuality"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I feel like I\'m 100 years old. I can\'t tell you what I did today. I can\'t tell you what I did for seven years. I can\'t tell you. It happens so seamlessly - I\'m just floating along and seven years go by.', '"Today,Feel,Floating"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I had really bad obsessive-compulsive disorder. At its worst, I was compelled to leave my house at three o\'clock in the morning and go out in the alley because I just knew that the paper-towel roll I threw in the recycling bin was uncomfortable, like it was lying the wrong way, and I would be down in the garbage."', '"Morning,Bad,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"For me, the best times are always going to be the most intense, the ones with the highest highs and the lowest lows."', '"Best,Me,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I\'m not the Queen. I\'m not a huge superstar; I don\'t get paparazzi around me.', '"Me,Queen,Paparazzi"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I was told so many times when I was a kid, \'I can\'t be friends with you, you\'re too intense, you\'re too sad all the time.\' I really thought that when I made the first album that everyone would understand me, all the people who weren\'t my friends would become my friends."', '"Sad,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I can bake. I made myself some nice French fries once. But otherwise I just eat out. Lots of salad bars.', '"Myself,I Can,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"When you\'re surrounded by all these people, it can be even lonelier than when you\'re by yourself. You can be in a huge crowd, but if you don\'t feel like you can trust anybody or talk to anybody, you feel like you\'re really alone."', '"Alone,Trust,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I walk my dog at dawn because I don\'t like people to be around.', '"Walk,People,Dawn"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'Five years from now I\'m probably going to look back on the things I\'m doing and cringe.', '"Look,Back,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I got all my work done to graduate in two months and then they were like, I\'m sorry, you have to take driver\'s ed. I just kind of went, Oh, forget it."', '"Work,Graduation,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I used to get a shiver if I thought about holding balloons, because I was scared of floating away."', '"Floating,Scared,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I just tend to do things to myself that I don\'t realize I\'m doing. Sometimes I bite my lip so that it splits and hurts, and yet I can\'t stop. And sometimes I\'d play shows on the last run, I\'d scratch my neck while I was singing, and I\'d horrified to see these red streaks of blood after."', '"Myself,Singing,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I don\'t go on lunch dates with friends. I hear about people having dinner parties, but I never do that. I\'m not really human."', '"Lunch,Dinner,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'The age thing really bugs me. Do people have more of a right to not like what I say because I\'m 19?', '"Age,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I got drunk when I was five. Everybody gets drunk before they\'re 21.', '"Drunk,Five,Everybody"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I don\'t know if anybody wants to mix their politics with their entertainment.', '"Politics,Entertainment,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'The way I feel about music is that there is no right and wrong. Only true and false.', '"Music,True,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I have a very steadfast tendency to parent myself, to monitor my development into the person I want to be. I\'ve tried to keep the corruption minimal."', '"Myself,Corruption,Development"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I want to be like the patron saint of reality.', '"Reality,Want,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I\'ve gone through stages where I hate my body so much that I won\'t even wear shorts and a bra in my house because if I pass a mirror, that\'s the end of my day."', '"Mirror,Hate,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"If I respect myself and believe in what I\'m doing, no one can touch me."', '"Respect,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'You can live your whole life in your brain and not experience what\'s around you. You go crazy that way.', '"Life,Experience,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I think I\'m better at live shows than I used to be because I\'m way more comfortable with the uncomfortable pauses between songs. Now, rather than trying to talk or do a costume change, I\'ll use those moments for myself. I listen to what other people are playing, or just rest, or dance, even though I don\'t know how to."', '"Change,Myself,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"There were songs I would write about breaking up with somebody before I broke up with them, months and months before I broke up with them."', '"Up,About,Somebody"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'The quick success was a bit strange to get used to.', '"Success,Strange,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"How can you go wrong with two people in love? If a good boy loves a good girl, good. If a good boy loves another good boy, good. And if a good girl loves the goodness in good boys and good girls, then all you have is more goodness, and goodness has nothing to do with sexual orientation."', '"Love,Good,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"But I honestly don\'t read critics. My dad reads absolutely everything ever written about me. He calls me up to read ecstatic reviews, but I always insist that I can\'t hear them. If you give value to the good reviews, you have to give value to the criticism."', '"Good,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I resent limitations. I\'m going to be this way for a while.', '"Way,Limitations,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"If you want to see me cry, just come to a photo shoot."', '"Me,See,Cry"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I was so self-critical. I still am, but it\'s not as bad anymore."', '"Bad,Still,Self-Critical"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'Men are my bread and butter. It\'s what I live for! I have no shame about that.', '"Men,Live,Shame"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"As a person who performs on stage, it\'s good to be emotionally open. If you mess with someone when they are in that state, it\'s like you\'re messing with an animal when it\'s eating."', '"Good,Eating,Animal"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"When I was a kid - 10, 11, 12, 13 - the thing I wanted most in the world was a best friend. I wanted to be important to people; to have people that understood me. I wanted to just be close to somebody."', '"Best,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Sometimes interviews are fun and good conversations, but stuff like photo shoots and appearances at places where you have to meet a lot of people - I was never really made for this kind of stuff."', '"Good,Fun,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I also just accept that I might never want to write a song again.', '"Song,Accept,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Now I feel like whatever I do, no one can hurt me. I cannot be violated, I cannot be humiliated, I cannot be disregarded, I cannot be disrespected."', '"Me,Feel,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I\'m here because of what I write. Obviously, I must know something."', '"Know,Because,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I don\'t think what I look like is relevant.', '"Look,Think,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"The worst pain in the world is shame. I spend a lot of time trying to not do anything bad to anyone, but you can\'t live your life and not hurt people."', '"Life,Time,Pain"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I don\'t care what people do. I don\'t care how people remember my albums. I do them for my own reasons.', '"Care,Remember,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'Everybody sees me as this sullen and insecure little thing. Those are just the sides of me that I feel it\'s necessary to show because no one else seems to be showing them.', '"Me,Feel,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I dare anybody to look at me and say I\'m anorexic. I\'m so totally not.', '"Look,Me,Dare"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I caved in to what people wanted me to do. I thought that they weren\'t going to like me if I didn\'t.', '"Me,People,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I\'m not a control freak.', '"Control,Freak,Control Freak"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'What\'s really good is African drum music.', '"Good,Music,Drum"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I wasn\'t very ambitious as a child. I\'m still not.', '"Child,Still,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'The only reason that it takes me seven years to do stuff is because I just don\'t really have a plan.', '"Me,Reason,Plan"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I never went to concerts when I was a kid, so I never knew if what I was doing onstage was right."', '"Never,Doing,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"You know, I\'ve always thought that it would be really funny if somebody made a romantic comedy where absolutely everything went well from beginning to end."', '"Funny,Romantic,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I know what my job is: I write the songs, I sing them, I play them on the piano."', '"Know,Job,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I really don\'t think anything I do is a mistake. It could be if I didn\'t learn from it.', '"Mistake,Anything,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I don\'t want to give any advice to a 19-year-old, because I want a 19-year-old to make mistakes and learn from them. Make mistakes, make mistakes, make mistakes. Just make sure they\'re your mistakes."', '"Advice,Mistakes,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"If I have one success in my relationship history, it\'s with the people who listen to my music. I think that they\'ll be there with me forever, and I\'ll be there with them forever. And I\'m totally satisfied with that."', '"Success,History,Relationship"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I can\'t remember writing any of the songs that I\'ve written.', '"Remember,Writing,Any"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I wrote \'Criminal\' in 45 minutes when everyone else went to lunch because I had to have a hit. I can force myself to do the work, but only if someone is right up behind me."', '"Work,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Hearing my songs in public freaks me out a bit. There was one restaurant I really liked in L.A., but I had to stop going there when they started playing my music. It felt kinda awkward."', '"Music,Restaurant,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I don\'t have a big thing about leaving my mark or being historic.', '"Big,Leaving,About"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"No, I\'ve never wanted kids. But I do read about parenting a lot."', '"Parenting,Never,About"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I was never somebody who grew up going, \'I really want to be a singer in a band,\' and I never had any ambition toward anything, really."', '"Ambition,Never,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I would really like to go back to school. I would love it now.', '"Love,School,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"In a strange way, I\'m way more comfortable onstage than anywhere else."', '"Way,Comfortable,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I\'m a really good parent to myself sometimes, and I do things that make me learn and grow."', '"Good,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I wanted to write a happy song. I didn\'t know how.', '"Song,Know,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"You think you\'re looking at things all the time, but you\'re not looking at things, you\'re looking at what your brain is interpreting through light and color. And who knows what everybody else sees?"', '"Time,Brain,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"And if I\'m being honest, I don\'t think I have an ex-boyfriend who would have something mean to say about me."', '"Me,Mean,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I read on the Internet that I was dead.', '"Internet,Dead,Read"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I got a lot of problems, but I\'m really good at intuiting what I need to do to be happy with whatever I create. I know when to stop myself, I know when to start, I know when to leave something alone. I guess I just kind of indulge that completely, and so I just take my time."', '"Alone,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', 'I\'ve never been to the websites. It\'s a lot healthier for me to keep out of the conversations about me.', '"Me,Never,Websites"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Because for whatever reason, even though I want to stay home all the time and be left alone, I want to tell the world who I am now."', '"Alone,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I\'m incredibly impressed by people who organize to achieve a goal, and believe that they can make a difference and then go ahead and do just that. I think it\'s incredible."', '"Believe,People,Make A Difference"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I\'m not used to not having enough time to live with the songs. Usually, if I write something, I live with it for a little while."', '"Time,Live,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"I got into therapy in the fifth grade because I said in a sarcastic way that I was going to kill myself, and they didn\'t get it then. Nothing\'s changed."', '"Myself,Way,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"In a sense it\'s a lot crazier when you\'re on the road and it\'s a lot less stable, but it\'s actually really healthy for me because it keeps me from isolating, which I tend to do a lot."', '"Me,Road,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4e', '"Our ancestors always thought of the worst thing that could happen, and that\'s why we\'re alive."', '"Alive,Worst,Ancestors"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'Barbecue is to North Carolina as the hot dog is to New York.', '"Hot,Barbecue,New"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"The unsaid is a powerful tool. It invites the reader into the narrative, filling in gaps, interpreting silences and half-finished sentences, and seeing the hidden fear in someone\'s eye."', '"Fear,Someone,Hidden"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"I can\'t think whether I\'ve actually interviewed the widow of a crime suspect. Obviously, I\'ve interviewed members of the families of people who\'ve been accused of things."', '"People,Widow,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'The imagination is such as powerful tool: suggestion is all you need. People fill in gaps.', '"Imagination,People,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"The righting of historic wrongs has chimed with something fundamental in me since I was a young reader. I love the forensic skills, the psychological insights, and the sheer bloody-mindedness of various detectives - professional or accidental - inching toward the truth of a long-buried secret."', '"Love,Truth,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"We may like to pretend otherwise, but we all have thoughts we don\'t want anyone else to know, things we\'ve done that would change the way people feel about us, or parts of our lives that we would rather forget."', '"Change,Thoughts,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"I like my villains clever, deep, and driven by pure evil."', '"Clever,Evil,Pure"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"The success of \'The Widow\' meant there were expectations for the second book from the first word, and it has created a completely different writing experience. Not to say I haven\'t enjoyed writing \'The Child,\' but I confess there were times when I felt as if I was wrenching it out of my body with bloodied fingernails!"', '"Success,Experience,Expectations"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"As a reporter, I spent a great deal of time in court. During brief breaks in testimony, I would often look at the spouse, usually the wife, of the accused. I began to wonder how listening to the details of a crime purportedly committed by your spouse would affect that person\'s view of her husband."', '"Time,Great,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"I know I love a novel with an unreliable narrator, and I think many readers do as well."', '"Love,Know,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"When you think about it, psychological thrillers often involve extraordinary events happening to ordinary people."', '"People,Extraordinary,Events"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"It\'s a wonderful experience to be reading a story and think you\'ve got things all figured out, and then suddenly, it all goes upside-down on you."', '"Experience,Story,Wonderful"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"Since reading \'Sophie\'s Choice,\' I have been haunted by the agonizing idea of choosing between two children."', '"Children,Choice,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"When you are a journalist, you are always looking for the next story. It might come from a phone call from a contact or an unanswered question you spot in someone else\'s article."', '"Looking,Phone Call,Phone"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"The emotions, responsibilities - and the pain - of motherhood are unique to each of us with children. Ask any woman, and she will have her own story to tell."', '"Pain,Emotions,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'I chose to write from different perspectives despite its complexity because it is what I have always done as a journalist.', '"Done,Always,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"Once you write a book, you hand it over to the readers, and it\'s their book then. They\'re so involved. They ask questions about details that I haven\'t even thought about."', '"Details,Questions,Book"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'It\'s amazing to me that journalists are held in such low esteem.', '"Amazing,Me,Low"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"When you start writing fiction, you have to learn to invent, and it\'s very hard at the beginning to stop relying on facts and what you\'ve heard."', '"Facts,Beginning,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'Mental health is something that I\'m very interested in.', '"Health,Mental Health,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"When I first became a journalist, people said, \'Oh, that must be interesting.\' They saw it as slightly glamorous, slightly edgy. They wanted to know more."', '"People,Glamorous,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"A lot of people think journalists are criminals, and there are some who haven\'t helped us. But the media is essential for democratic society."', '"Society,Media,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"As a journalist, your words are regularly read by lots of people, but they\'re not your words: they\'re someone else\'s. You\'re quoting people."', '"Words,People,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'Writing is not just about putting words on a page. Ideas have to cook first.', '"Words,Ideas,First"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"Garrison Keillor\'s \'Lake Wobegon\' books create a world I can immerse myself in over and over. I love the deadpan humour, the warmth, and the wonderful characters in The Sidetrack Tap. I discovered them when I was about 30, starting with \'Leaving Home\' and \'We Are Still Married,\' and fell in love with the place and those flat Midwestern vowels."', '"Love,Home,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"For me, there has always been the irresistible lure of a secret."', '"Me,Always,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"It was this fascination with hidden lives, I suspect, that led me to journalism; seeking to uncover the truth about people became a job."', '"Truth,Me,Journalism"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"For most of us, our protective lies or omissions are so insignificant that being found out would be only mildly embarrassing. But for some of us, our secret may threaten to destroy everything. And that is food and drink to a novelist."', '"Food,Everything,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'The secrets of small towns have fascinated writers and readers since the first psychological thriller was penned.', '"Secrets,Small,First"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', 'Donna Tartt is a genius.', 'Genius', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"As a journalist, I\'ve been a professional watcher, picking up the body language and verbal tics that make us individuals and interesting to others."', '"Body,Language,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"Over the years, I\'ve interviewed the victims, the guilty, the famous, the important, and the ordinary people affected by tragedy or good fortune. But strangely, it is not always the people in the spotlight that have stayed with me. It is often those on the periphery, the bit players in the drama, that continue to haunt."', '"Good,Famous,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"It is a sad truth that apprenticeships fell out of favour in Britain in the Seventies and Eighties, when the manufacturing industries shed jobs and the construction industry went into decline."', '"Truth,Sad,Construction"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd4f', '"Yes, there are bad apples, but I do feel journalists do a good job, often in very difficult circumstances."', '"Good,Difficult,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My own valuation moment: When I started \'Antiques Roadshow,\' John Benjamin looked at my engagement ring, which is Victorian. I sat there as a visitor would and he dated it, talked me through the stone, which is an opal, and which mine it would have been from."', '"Moment,Me,Stone"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"You can\'t beat a good millefeuille, which is basically a posh custard slice. Yum!"', '"Good,Beat,Posh"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If I were to say anything to my 18-year-old self, it would be, \'Loosen up. Chill out.\'"', '"Chill,Self,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Brexit can tend to be a dialogue of the deaf.', '"Deaf,Brexit,Dialogue"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"The atmosphere in the newsroom could be pretty poisonous. When I arrived, the people who worked on the \'Six\' were sitting there slagging off what had gone out on the \'One.\' I thought: \'What is this place? And what are you saying about me?\'"', '"Me,People,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I think the BBC has come a long way in equal pay. I think it\'s come the furthest of all in the representation of women on screen.', '"Women,Long,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I was born in Singapore, but I left at four so memories are hazy."', '"Memories,Born,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I love \'The Master And Margarita\' by Mikhail Bulgakov, which is about repression in Soviet Russia in the 1930s."', '"Love,Master,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I think having a healthy distrust of authority is a good thing, within certain parameters, obviously."', '"Good,Authority,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I think it\'s important to rebel a little bit.', '"Important,Rebel,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'m astonished at the freedom with which a depressingly large number of men feel they can just say what they want and write the most hideously misogynistic stuff about women.', '"Freedom,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I love \'Chicago,\' I love the musical and the movie and I thought Catherine Zeta-Jones was amazing."', '"Love,Amazing,Thought"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I couldn\'t imagine life without Radio 4.', '"Life,Radio,Imagine"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'ve chosen not to go to Sky or ITV because the programmes I\'ve made at the BBC, I want to carry on making."', '"Sky,Go,Chosen"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If you\'re in people\'s living-rooms, via the television, it\'s what happens. You\'re more noticeable. But I\'m not aware that anyone has said I pay a lower rate of tax. I don\'t. I pay my full share of tax, believe you me."', '"Me,Believe,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Think Oman, and you think desert. But what we found was mile after mile of barren, spiky rubble, cliffs of jutting sharp rocks, unrelieved by a single piece of vegetation or water. We drove for hours across what felt like the surface of the moon. We saw goats foraging but couldn\'t work out what they could possibly be eating."', '"Work,Water,Moon"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Most visitors to Iceland tend to spend just a few hours in Reykjavik before moving on to the geological wonders beyond. I think they are missing out.', '"Moving On,Moving,Beyond"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I talk about feminism being a spectrum.', '"Talk,About,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I haven\'t done Botox. Although there are a few women on screen who do, and if you don\'t do it, which I don\'t, you look pretty rough by comparison."', '"Women,Look,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I conquered my phobia of camping, although I doubt I\'ll be pitching my tent at a muddy festival any time soon."', '"Time,Doubt,Pitching"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'m not tough. I\'m just not a retiring violet when it comes to airing my opinions.', '"Tough,Opinions,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If I want to watch things I\'m on, I end up watching on my own."', '"End,Watching,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Question Time\' had been on my fantasy bucket list for some time. Of all the jobs in broadcasting that\'s the job I knew I wanted to do.', '"Time,Fantasy,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"As an army marches on its stomach, I vacation on mine. And for that reason, among others, I found myself in holiday heaven in Singapore."', '"Myself,Heaven,Holiday"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"When I started presenting I\'d get invited to red carpet events and I went to a few premieres. But pretty soon I thought, \'Life\'s too short.\'"', '"Life,Red,Short"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Coming to Rajasthan had been my idea, my dream. In the weeks before we arrived, I had tried and failed on numerous occasions to enthuse my family with the joys of travel in India; reading bits from the guidebooks, telling the children about the history of the Mughals, insisting to my daughter that she really would enjoy curry if it was in India."', '"Family,History,Travel"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"The one good thing about jet lag when you fly to the United States is that you wake up so madly early, you can beat everyone else to the big tourist attractions and miss the queues."', '"Good,Fly,Wake Up"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Don\'t ask me the secret to a good long-term relationship - I have no idea! Honestly, I think it\'s just luck."', '"Relationship,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Outside certain parameters, I don\'t consider myself that serious a person."', '"Myself,Serious,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"The best thing, on \'Question Time,\' is when the reality confronts the rhetoric."', '"Best,Time,Reality"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I am a simple soul.', '"Simple,Soul,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I had done debate programmes before and quite often you go into them thinking: \'I might need to build some energy in the room.\' \'On Question Time,\' the reverse is true. A lot of the time, I am just trying to not have it turn into a slanging match."', '"Time,Thinking,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I think of myself as a journalist first and foremost.', '"Myself,First,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'m all for a passionate debate, and sometimes things can be heated, which is fine, up to a point. As long as we remember that we are human beings."', '"Long,Remember,Debate"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Antiques Roadshow\' is a public service. It reflects the nation back to itself, as does \'Question Time.\'"', '"Time,Service,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If you take over a programme from a longstanding incumbent, not everyone\'s going to like it."', '"Everyone,Like,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"In my twenties, I was virulently opposed to anyone commenting on my appearance, lest it come at the expense of my ability."', '"Appearance,Ability,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Antiques Roadshow\' was the first job I had taken since my children were born that took me away from them consistently over a period of time. That was a big adjustment for all of us.', '"Time,Me,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Family is the priority. Your job never loves you back, that\'s the way I look at it."', '"Family,Look,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'m all about the story. And the stories I remember tend to be the ones of sorrow, or family history, or revelation of the self."', '"Family,History,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'m used to doing a lot of live broadcasting.', '"Live,Doing,Broadcasting"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'m always disappointed by women who say they prefer working with men. What is that all about? I love working with women, I love the company of women."', '"Love,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I wasn\'t born into money, and you never know when that money\'s going to stop coming in."', '"Money,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'m quite famously frugal.', '"Quite,Frugal"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"The thing is, if you come on the \'Roadshow\' we are not going to humiliate you. The thing about the \'Antiques Roadshow\' is not to humiliate people."', '"People,Come,About"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Have I ever presented a programme I don\'t watch? Well, I\'ve done loads of programmes that no one else watched!"', '"Done,Well,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"To me it\'s always been a no-brainer. Maybe I\'m just simplistic about it, but if you believe in equality of opportunity, and want to champion equality of opportunity, that makes you a feminist."', '"Equality,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I still remember watching \'Antiques Roadshow\' as a child with my parents, on a Sunday night, sitting in our 1970s living room."', '"Night,Parents,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I collect things called \'samplers\' which are Victorian pieces of needlework usually done by children in a workhouse to show that they have a skill which can be used in service, stitching household linen or that kind of thing. I think they\'re very humble and very beautiful."', '"Beautiful,Humble,Skill"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I backpacked around Thailand when I was a university student and have wanted to return ever since.', '"University,Student,Return"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Thailand was a revelation to me; the landscapes, the culture, the food and the people."', '"Food,Culture,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'ve been on camels before, lumbering slowly through the desert - not hugely exciting, but I enjoyed the \'Lawrence of Arabia\' vibe."', '"Desert,Through,Enjoyed"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I don\'t particularly like being told what to do.', '"Like,Being,Particularly"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Muscat itself is a mixture of impersonal modern buildings, shopping malls, mosques, traditional souks, tarmac and sand."', '"Sand,Shopping,Buildings"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'d set out to Oman in search of luxury with culture and family-friendly adventure thrown in. And I found it.', '"Culture,Search,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Within less than an hour of arriving in Singapore, it was clear we had arrived in a country where eating has been elevated to the status of a national pastime."', '"Eating,Country,Singapore"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"No matter how beautiful a spot I find myself in, if the food ain\'t up to much, I won\'t enjoy myself."', '"Food,Myself,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If you crave a bit of adventure and the unknown, Singapore is not for you."', '"Adventure,Unknown,Singapore"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Well, not everyone wants to lead the kind of life I lead."', '"Life,Everyone,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I don\'t know anything about antiques. I do buy them now, but I have a little knowledge, and great enthusiasm."', '"Knowledge,Great,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My father was MD of Unilever, so we followed him around the world."', '"World,Father,Around"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"With two older brothers, I was a tomboy in one sense, but on the other hand I really loved dolls. My brothers weren\'t very happy when I nicked their Action Men to play with my dolls and they were appalled when I made them kiss my Barbies."', '"Men,Action,Kiss"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My Duke of Edinburgh interview for his 90th in June 2011 was not one of my successes. I knew what to expect: there were some very uncomfortable moments and put-downs, but I think it made for entertaining viewing."', '"Uncomfortable,Interview,June"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Of course, I\'d love to be regarded as a voice of authority."', '"Love,Voice,Authority"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'ve worked hard, but I\'ve been lucky too."', '"Hard,Lucky,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"When I started in news on the \'Six O\'Clock,\' I was 36 and felt very inexperienced."', '"News,Six,Felt"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'The audience is an absolutely critical part of \'Question Time\' and selecting that audience is a big and very important job every week. What we need to do every week without fail is make the audience politically representative of the picture across the nation.', '"Time,Picture,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"The standards by which a woman\'s appearance is judged on the news are different to men, there\'s no question about that. Our clothes are different, for starters, they\'re much more varied, they\'re commented upon, there\'s no question about that. But do you have to be really good-looking? I don\'t think that\'s true."', '"Men,News,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"Really, I\'ve been at the BBC too long and have spent too much time out on the road to worry about being judged as a clothes horse."', '"Time,Long,Road"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I was the first person in my family to go to university so it was quite a big deal for us.', '"Family,Person,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My kids once said, \'What would you do if you hadn\'t got us?\' I replied, \'I\'d be more successful and I\'d have more friends, but I wouldn\'t be as happy.\'"', '"Happy,More,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"There is a thing about women, in particular, being endlessly grateful for the opportunities in life, rather than saying, \'I\'m here because I\'m good.\'"', '"Life,Women,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I saw \'The Theory of Everything,\' which I loved, but I\'m afraid I hardly ever get to go to the cinema."', '"Cinema,Everything,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I was at a film premiere that George Clooney was attending and I was very star-struck. We weren\'t having a long conversation or anything, but I was definitely slightly in awe of him."', '"Long,Conversation,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"This is going to make me sound 100 years old, but I really loved David Cassidy in \'The Partridge Family.\'"', '"Family,Me,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I really like sitting down with my daughter to watch programmes like \'Call the Midwife,\' \'24 hours in A&E,\' \'One Born Every Minute\' and \'Our Girl.\' It\'s just the two of us, which is really nice."', '"Born,Daughter,24 Hours"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"On \'Question Time,\' I\'ve noticed great anger from the audience. When we discuss Brexit, emotions range from white-hot fury to cold, grey apathy. As soon as we move off Brexit, debate is much more nuanced and considered."', '"Time,Anger,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"After \'Question Time,\' I find my mind is racing. So I try to watch something that\'s a million miles away from all that, like \'Poldark\' or \'Call the Midwife\' or \'Derry Girls.\'"', '"Time,Mind,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I don\'t go into the newsroom and people start salivating. I can\'t think of anything further from the truth.', '"Truth,People,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I remember my dad saying to me, \'But Fiona don\'t you want to go and do the dramatic society. You can still do your women\'s groups as well.\' And I said, \'Dad, feminism is a way of life! It\'s not a hobby!\'"', '"Life,Women,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Age is definitely an issue for women in TV. There comes a point - especially if you\'re a woman - when your career just falls off a cliff. I\'m not being self-pitying. That\'s just the way it is.', '"Women,Age,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I learnt a salutary lesson when I was being hired for the \'Six O\'Clock News\' and others were being fired, people who I thought were great, like Jill Dando. Letting her go was a big mistake, in my view. But that is probably going to be me one day - I\'ll read about it in the press and that will be that."', '"Great,View,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"You don\'t have doubts when you get offered \'Question Time.\' You think, thank you very much."', '"Time,Thank You,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"There\'s not much opportunity to learn to read the news. By and large, you either can or you can\'t do it pretty much straight away."', '"Opportunity,News,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I have a few grey hairs. I dye them. I don\'t let them show when I\'m reading the news.', '"News,Grey,Reading"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'My father John taught me about hard work and the importance of manners.', '"Work,Hard Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'Pudding is my favourite part of any meal and I always have one if I can manage it.', '"Always,I Can,Meal"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I wouldn\'t consider cosmetic surgery.', '"Surgery,Consider,Cosmetic"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"There are a million and one things I\'d love to get stuck into. Travel, finally getting to spend some time with the family. And I\'d love to become a magistrate."', '"Love,Family,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'You don\'t present a show like \'Crimewatch\' without developing a real respect for the justice system in this country.', '"Respect,Justice,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I\'ve been a journalist for too long to stop calling myself a journalist, and also when I\'m doing \'Fake or Fortune?\' I\'m going through a rigorous investigation."', '"Myself,Long,Fake"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'I\'m very fortunate in the things I\'ve done and I\'ve worked really hard at them. It\'s always ultimately up to the viewers whether they like it or not.', '"Done,Always,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', 'The BBC is a huge part of the nation\'s cultural life.', '"Life,Nation,Huge"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"People are more than two-dimensional, and again I think the complexities in life, and in one\'s makeup, grow as you get older, partly through experience."', '"Life,Experience,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My mum, who died in 2011, was the most loving mother you could ask for. She was very compassionate, always a good listener, and her love was a constant throughout my life. She was very sympathetic, kind and understanding and I think these values can be underrated."', '"Life,Love,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"My parents\' set-up was very traditional, whereas that\'s not the life I\'ve chosen to lead."', '"Life,Parents,Chosen"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"They\'re all good-looking men - I can\'t think of a male presenter who isn\'t a good-looking bloke - but, you know, they\'re not judged by their suits and ties."', '"Men,Know,Good-Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"I met someone with a title on my first day, Baronet von Something, and I thought: \'Look at me, I\'ve really grafted. Who are these people who have just waltzed into Oxford? I don\'t want to hang out with those people. They\'re nothing like me.\'"', '"Look,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"When both my parents were unwell I was in that situation that will be very familiar to many women. I had young children in one part of the country, and elderly unwell parents in another. I was in a constant state of guilt. Was I there enough for my mother? Was I there enough for my children?"', '"Women,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd50', '"If you work and you want to see your children, something\'s got to give and for me, it\'s my social life."', '"Life,Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I feel like, sometimes, when things are just handed to people, in a way, right away, you don\'t get a sense of what the rejection and the struggle is like that comes along with life."', '"Life,Struggle,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I stopped watching horror movies after I watched \'Candyman\' when I was - I don\'t know, fifteen or something. I remember my sister rented it, \'Candyman,\' and it really, really scared me. And so it was only after I found myself in a horror film that I really went back and kind of rediscovered the genre."', '"Movies,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I have a different relationship with Chucky because he\'s been on top of my bookshelf in the corner of my living room for my entire life. He was a great tool for scaring friends, and when I see him in different theme parks I\'ve been to, or in commercials, my heart swells a little bit, and I\'m like, \'Aww! It\'s my Chucky!\'"', '"Life,Relationship,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', 'Chucky is absolutely still a puppet. He will remain to be.', '"Will,He,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I did an improv that was one of the most exhilarating ten minutes of my entire life. I mean, when you\'re doing it, you forget yourself."', '"Life,Yourself,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', 'I feel like acting is a ton of fun. It\'s the freest and most alive you can be.', '"Fun,Feel,Alive"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I think if a horror movie is really scary, you\'ll think about it for weeks, and there\'s something kind of fun about that - about our art, really."', '"Art,Fun,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd51', '"I actually think that\'s true, that we kind of create our own hell."', '"Hell,True,Create"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"I actually got started in acting when I was in pre-school. I was really into dance and performing, so my mom had me in dance classes, and then I got involved in a local theater company."', '"Mom,Me,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"I have an hourglass shape, and I think it\'s important to understand your body type and your personality type. Then make whatever is on trend and in fashion work for you."', '"Work,Personality,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"I went to UCLA as pre-med. When I was there my freshman year, I auditioned for a play and got it, and I was so passionate. I just loved acting so much that I decided to switch majors and pursue acting."', '"Acting,Loved,Year"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"I definitely prefer working in comedy over drama, but at the same time, when it comes to comedy, I tend to prefer comedies that have a great sense of truth to them and that come from an honest place."', '"Truth,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"One of my favorite comedies is \'Groundhog Day\' and \'Scrooged.\' I love Bill Murray, and I think he\'s a great example of an actor who is funny."', '"Funny,Love,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd52', '"I have a lot of anxiety about the red carpet. As a woman, it\'s uncomfortable to be in a position in which people are judging you, looking at what you\'re wearing, and criticizing you - not necessarily in a negative way."', '"Negative,Woman,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The Cold War was obviously driven by a very intense ideological struggle that was very clearly defined.', '"War,Struggle,Cold"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The Russians thrive on misinformation and disinformation.', '"Thrive,Misinformation,Disinformation"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Russia was dependent on China growing and driving the demand for its commodities: oil, gas and minerals. China was an alternative to Europe."', '"Russia,Europe,Oil"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Putin has the ability to advance his interests in many different ways. Sometimes tactical diplomacy can help.', '"Diplomacy,Sometimes,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'President Putin and the Russian security services operate like a super PAC. They deploy millions of dollars to weaponize our own political opposition research and false narratives.', '"Political,Research,Security"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The Russians didn\'t invent partisan divides. The Russians haven\'t invented racism in the United States. But the Russians understand a lot of those divisions and they understand how to exploit them.', '"Understand,United,How"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I applied to Oxford in the \'80s and was invited to an interview. It was like a scene from \'Billy Elliot.\' People were making fun of me for my accent and the way I was dressed. It was the most embarrassing, awful experience I had ever had in my life."', '"Life,Experience,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"The real concern for the Russians is that they\'re going to get closed out, that there\'s gong to be a new \'Iron Curtain\'... for European expansion and all of its institutional forms."', '"New,Real,Concern"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Obama is under incredible pressure to supply arms to Ukraine.', '"Pressure,Incredible,Ukraine"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'President Trump understands that President Putin does not like to be insulted. Putin takes it very personally. He harbors a grudge. He doesn\'t forget. And he will find some way of getting some degree of revenge as a result of that.', '"Revenge,Result,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Russia and China thawed their frosty relationship in the 1990s and signed a friendship treaty in 2001, but China\'s rise has increased tensions in every regional relationship."', '"Friendship,Relationship,Rise"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'I don\'t want to suggest that Trump is emulating Putin. Trump is his own creation.', '"Creation,Own,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Calling Trump \'Putin\'s puppet\' is a sign of the weakness of the American political system. It appears so weak and fragile that outsiders can actually meddle about in it.', '"Political,American,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"And being forceful with the United States and not letting the United States have its way, is always good politics in the Russian domestic environment."', '"Politics,Good,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'There\'s no prospect that the Russians are going to send Snowden back. Snowden is in the land of spy swaps now. Putin is not going to give this guy up for nothing.', '"Nothing,Back,Land"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"For the United States, in particular, the South Caucasus has been a priority since the 1990s."', '"United,United States,1990s"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Russia doesn\'t want to have a return to the situation where it was the United States and say Israel, making determinations about whether there might be a strike against Iran if the negotiations over the nuclear weapons program weren\'t going in a direction that they wanted to."', '"Direction,Situation,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The refugee problem is definitely a disaster for the entire region. Putin - the refugee problem in Chechnya was largely contained inside of Russia itself although there were tens of thousands of Chechens who sought refuge across Europe. Putin wasn\'t swayed by that issue when it came to Chechnya.', '"Disaster,Russia,Inside"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Outside of the Moscow elite and a very small urban elite, Russia is one great big blue-collar country."', '"Great,Country,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I got a PhD from Harvard and a few years later, there was a girl from Sunderland who hadn\'t got into Oxford or Cambridge, even though she\'d got perfect A-levels. Harvard asked me to come and recruit her because I was recruited out of university by Harvard - they were trying to show that people could make it."', '"Me,Perfect,People"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'There is a good supply of Russia experts out there - people who have lived there with lots of good experience - but the demand has just not been there from government.', '"Experience,Good,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Ironically, from our perspective, Russia finds Iran a stabilizing force. This is because Iran provides a counterweight to all of the Sunni Muslim powers in the region, being predominantly Shia. And Putin actually sees, and the rest of the Russian leadership, sees Iran very much as a rational actor."', '"Leadership,Perspective,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'So Putin is not the dictator that he\'s often accused of being. He has to be very sensitive to public opinion.', '"Opinion,He,Sensitive"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'We have politicized the issue of Russia to a point that we can\'t have a sensible conversation about it.', '"Conversation,Russia,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'We\'ve got ourselves into a situation where government service is somehow seen to be a political act rather than an act of civic duty or of public service.', '"Government,Political,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"So with President Obama, he\'s a very different style. Very thoughtful, posed."', '"Style,Thoughtful,He"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The unfortunate truth is that Russia was the foreign power that systematically attacked our democratic institutions in 2016.', '"Truth,Power,Institutions"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'I can say with confidence that this country has offered for me opportunities I would never have had in England.', '"Confidence,Me,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I refuse to be part of an effort to legitimize an alternate narrative that the Ukrainian government is a U.S. adversary, and that Ukraine - not Russia - attacked us in 2016."', '"Government,Effort,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Because the more you engage with someone who is spreading untruths, the more validity you give to those untruths."', '"Someone,More,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'I know Kurt Volker definitely to be a man of integrity.', '"Man,Integrity,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'I grew up poor with a very distinctive working-class accent. In England in the 1980s and 1990s this would have impeded my professional advancement. This background has never set me back in America.', '"Me,America,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I am very confident based on all of the analysis that has been done - and, again, I don\'t want to start getting into intelligence matters - that the Ukrainian government did not interfere in our election in 2016."', '"Intelligence,Government,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"In the instance of Iran for Russia, Iran is a very important counterweight to the Sunni Muslim powers in the Gulf, but Russia\'s always been very concerned about potentially proselytizing and supporting groups inside of the Russian federation itself."', '"Important,Always,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Russia has always been very careful to try to balance the interest of the Gulf states and Iran off against each other.', '"Balance,Always,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"The capital city of Grozny in Chechnya was reduced completely to rubble, and Putin thought this was worthwhile because it kept the state together."', '"Together,City,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Absolutely everything I\'ve done - my research, my training, my book - was made possible due to Harvard opening doors and providing me with connections."', '"Me,Training,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'And Trump isn\'t exactly the most diplomatic of people.', '"People,Most,Exactly"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I tend to look at Trump as a real-estate mogul. You look at a building and say, \'I\'m just going to tear that down and build up something new.\' He\'s not exactly Mr. Preservationist."', '"Look,New,Building"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'My dad was a coal miner in County Durham.', '"Dad,Coal,Miner"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"I have worked hard and emigrated to the U.S., and I think of myself as working class but I\'m probably not any more."', '"Myself,Hard,More"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The people who run the giant companies and the government are all part of the same crowd.', '"Government,People,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Our basic problem is how do we stop the hot war on the ground in Ukraine, and not get into a more and more escalatory relationship with Putin."', '"War,Relationship,Hot"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Stop pyschoanalyzing Putin, and recognize that there is a certain mind set. The West must draw a line under \'Putinography\' and just get on with it."', '"Mind,Stop,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The whole purpose of Russian propaganda is to show that the U.S. and U.S. politics is filled with hubris and hypocrisy and to show it is not better than anyone else.', '"Politics,Purpose,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Putin operates like a super PAC, taking advantage of opportunities for negative campaigning. The purpose is to show that the U.S. has no moral authority."', '"Purpose,Negative,Authority"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"The idea is that Putin-Trump would be a win-win for the Kremlin, as they have mutual interests and alliances."', '"Mutual,Would,Win-Win"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"There is certainly this widespread anti-Americanism within the Russian elite, a feeling that the U.S. lost any moral high ground it could possibly have because of Iraq, Abu Ghraib, and increasing concern of U.S. intentions locally."', '"Lost,Elite,Ground"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"You could say that by standing up to Russia, the U.S. is finally getting some balls."', '"Standing,Russia,Balls"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The problem in Pankisi is an extension of broader problems throughout Georgia. The whole system is based on shady deals. The entire government is corrupt.', '"Government,Problems,System"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"People in Washington, D.C., may not be paying that much attention to what\'s happening in Chechnya, but people in Riyadh and Amman and elsewhere are."', '"People,Attention,May"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Everybody used to talk about Chechnya as a place, in the Russian imperial and Soviet periods, that was essentially governed by extended family and regional networks that substituted for older clan structures. But those networks have been destroyed."', '"Family,Place,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Chechnya was part of that whole wave of entities of the Soviet Union that had a very separate sense of identity, of political and social history, that set them apart from the rest of Russia."', '"History,Political,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Chechens need to be able to develop their own viable political society and regional economy whether they remain part of Russia or not.', '"Society,Political,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Tough sanctions would mean saying to BP, Exxon, Chevron, Shell, Boeing and Siemens that they can\'t do business in Russia."', '"Business,Tough,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'The Russian leadership doesn\'t operate in the same way as ours does. Informal networks have a much more important role to play than formal networks.', '"Leadership,Way,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Every military scenario that the Russians basically engage in their annual exercises, either on their western or eastern flank, always involved some kind of local revolt pulling in outside forces."', '"Always,Outside,Engage"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Trump knows how to play the media all on his own. He creates his own Twitter feed and uses it. He knows how to get the media\'s attention without the benefit of a state-controlled media. He does it all on his own. Trump understands how a free media works.', '"Free,Media,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"A U.S. president who is elected amid controversy and recrimination, reviled by a large segment of the electorate, and mired in domestic crises will be hard-pressed to forge a coherent foreign policy and challenge Russia."', '"Will,Challenge,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Putin is trying to create the best possible atmosphere for Russia.', '"Best,Create,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Putin has become the wild card in his own system.', '"Wild,Own,System"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'New ties between Russia and Japan would mark not only a breakthrough in their relations but also a significant shift in Northeast Asia\'s political dynamic.', '"Political,New,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Japan has good reasons for wanting to transform its relationship with Russia. Tokyo has openly expressed serious fears of a military confrontation with Beijing over China\'s claims to the Senkaku/Diaoyu Islands in the East China Sea.', '"Relationship,Good,Sea"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"Indeed, for Russia, inconsistency is an integral part of its foreign policy strategy, particularly under Putin."', '"Strategy,Indeed,Russia"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Few issues better illustrate the limits of the Obama administration\'s \'reset\' with Russia than the crisis in Syria.', '"Limits,Better,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"For Putin, Syria is all too reminiscent of Chechnya. Both conflicts pitted the state against disparate and leaderless opposition forces, which over time came to include extremist Sunni Islamist groups."', '"Time,Opposition,State"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', '"A desire to contain extremism is a major reason why Putin offered help to the United States in battling the Taliban in Afghanistan after 9/11. It is also why Russia maintains close relations with Shia Iran, which acts as a counterweight to Sunni powers."', '"Help,Why,Desire"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd53', 'Putin\'s treatment of Chechnya became a cautionary tale of what would happen to rebels and terrorists - and indeed to entire groups of people - if they threatened the Russian state.', '"People,Indeed,State"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"When I first decided I was going to have a go at writing a book - and really, it was a mid-life crisis - I was 39. I was in business with my husband; we had a very busy lifestyle and quite a hectic schedule running this flourishing business in travel, and I found myself waking up and realising that I didn\'t want to do this anymore."', '"Business,Travel,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:45:00', '2023-05-29 11:45:00'),
	('392992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"For me, a great fantasy is real people, a world I recognise, human struggle and magic. You\'ve got to have magic to make a fantasy work. But I like my magic to be subtle. I don\'t want magic coming out of the hands of wizards. I want it to be pervading, sinister somehow."', '"Work,Great,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"Readers want to have the confidence that you understand the era in which the book is set, so for \'The Perfumer\'s Secret,\' I needed to know everything about the First World War from a French perspective. I had to understand those people and that town in 1914."', '"War,Confidence,World"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"I don\'t see myself as an artist, as a writer. The sort of writing that I do, which is popular fiction, it\'s work. I have contracts to fulfil, and I have deadlines to meet."', '"Work,Myself,See"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"Fantasy was something I\'d read as a child. And, in fact, my teachers despaired a little bit because I refused to give up Enid Blyton. Then I walked through the wardrobe with C. S. Lewis, and I don\'t think I actually have returned fully from the wardrobe. So, fantasy was something that was in my life from quite young."', '"Life,My Life,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', 'We travel a lot from Australia and deliberately route ourselves through the U.A.E. because my whole family loves the place.', '"Family,Travel,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd54', '"What I find is that it\'s the middle-aged authors who have lived a life who have the most important, interesting voices. They just need someone to give them the key to unlock the door."', '"Life,Door,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"Also, an area that interests me - and it will probably take years to state what I mean - is the period of the rise of democracy, with Tom Paine, which is around the turn of the 18th century into the 19th."', '"Democracy,Me,Rise"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('392999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"Even when they have nothing, the Irish emit a kind of happiness, a joy."', '"Happiness,Joy,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I find it incredibly tedious, hate that it murders itself with its own conservative pomposity."', '"Hate,Own,Conservative"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"My mother adores singing and plays piano. My uncle was a phenomenal pianist. My brother John is a double bassist. I used to play the piano, badly, and cello. My brother Peter played violin."', '"Singing,Violin,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"To be honest I live among the English and have always found them to be very honest in their business dealings. They are noble, hard-working and anxious to do the right thing. But joy eludes them, they lack the joy that the Irish have."', '"Business,Joy,Do The Right Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'Acting doesn\'t have to be threadbare misery all the time.', '"Time,Acting,Misery"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'Every generation is obsessed with the decade before they were born.', '"Generation,Born,Decade"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I would say the next imminent hot writers are often the writers from the decade before you were born.', '"Hot,Born,Next"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I loathe bad theater and most theatre is very bad because it\'s repetitious, unexciting and, dangerously, it is sometimes praised for those things."', '"Bad,Sometimes,Theatre"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I just think that things should be allowed to run their course, and not turned into a Disney ride."', '"Ride,Things,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I\'m not afraid of chaos and I\'m happy talking to strangers. I really love not knowing where I\'m going.', '"Love,Chaos,Strangers"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I certainly had no intention of playing a man.', '"Man,Intention,Playing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"So I just play the character, I play the lines."', '"Character,Play,Lines"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"Once you\'ve done one style, you leave it for a while."', '"Style,Done,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'Theater dates very quickly.', '"Theater,Very,Dates"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'The word democracy has no meaning. Duty has gone. Only rights remain.', '"Democracy,Duty,Meaning"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'This whole tribal loyalty seems to have gone.', '"Loyalty,Gone,Tribal"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"There was no professional theater in Cork, but still I did a lot of performing."', '"Professional,Still,Did"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'A lot of Irish people perform. They perform in drawing rooms. They sing songs and they play piano.', '"People,Drawing,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"The energy released by it is enormous and it becomes quite addictive, the power between the audience and the actor."', '"Power,Energy,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'People who are good at film have a relationship with the camera.', '"Relationship,Good,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'Theater is dangerously open to repetition. It\'s exciting when you hit on a new way.', '"Way,New,Repetition"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I take the theater seriously in that I loathe it, I\'m bored by it."', '"Seriously,Bored,Take"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I can hardly decide what plays I should be in.', '"I Can,Decide,Should"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'There is a great relief in experiencing the worst vicariously.', '"Great,Worst,Relief"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I think America becomes more disgruntled by going to the movies and having an endlessly good time at them.', '"Time,Good,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I had a ball doing Harry Potter.', '"Doing,Ball,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'One moment cannot be the most important.', '"Moment,Important,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'My mother taught me to read.', '"Me,Mother,Taught"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'Irish people are educated not only about artistry but local history.', '"History,People,Educated"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'There\'s something about the Irish that is remarkable.', '"Something,About,Irish"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'There once was a demographic survey done to determine if money was connected to happiness and Ireland was the only place where this did not turn out to be true.', '"Happiness,Money,True"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"The Americans are very clear, and obsessed with nouns."', '"Clear,Very,Obsessed"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I would love to write the story of my upbringing in Ireland.', '"Love,Story,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I enjoy making films, but my heart is in the stage. Every night you have to be on. There\'s no second take."', '"Heart,Night,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"Like a lot of Irish households we read a lot of Irish history. It was almost Soviet, raising the next generation with a mythic view of their history."', '"History,View,Generation"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"Honestly, I get more recognized for \'Three Men and a Little Lady\' than \'Harry Potter\'."', '"Men,Lady,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'A relationship is sent by God and accident.', '"God,Relationship,Accident"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"I\'m not on the run from anything and I\'m not at all clear about what I\'m running towards. But as some great writer put it, I want to be certain that when I arrive at death, I\'m totally exhausted."', '"Death,Great,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', '"And by endlessly sanitizing our feelings, we actually feed a disgruntled nation."', '"Feelings,Nation,Feed"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd55', 'I once saw my mother playing Mary Magdalene in a parish event. But she had to put the role aside in order to go and front the choir who were singing at the same occasion. She left the stage halfway through the Crucifixion.', '"Singing,Mother,Halfway"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"There\'s a restaurant I go to whenever I can called The Richmond Cafe. It\'s a little Thai restaurant owned by a group of Thai women - I think they\'re all a family, and they\'re just really, really nice, and they make amazing massaman curry."', '"Family,Women,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"I knew it was called \'Dunkirk,\' Christopher Nolan was directing it, and it was a war film. That was all anyone knew."', '"War,Film,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"My \'Dunkirk\' co-star Harry Styles deals with some crazy fan stuff, but he\'s a very down-to-earth, lovely, funny guy."', '"Funny,Crazy,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"I think you can overthink dealing with fame. To an extent, you\'ve got to put yourself out there, but I feel like your work should really speak for itself, and I don\'t feel the need to go and make everyone like me because, to be honest, I\'m not looking to be friends with the world. I\'d much rather people watch the things that I\'m in."', '"Work,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"I don\'t really think much about how I would have fared in the Second World War. It\'s a topic that has to be treated with respect and subtlety, and you can\'t just go in all guns blazing and make an epic action film."', '"War,Respect,World"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"\'HIM\' is much more of a British, coming-of-age series, while \'Stranger Things\' is very obviously a sci-fi drama."', '"Drama,Stranger,More"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"I like to think I\'m fairly grounded, and I have friends who will very happily tell me if I\'m ever being big-headed. I know things will change. But I\'m hoping it\'s nothing too drastic."', '"Change,Me,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', 'I\'m not really a green juice kind of guy. I like feeling downtrodden and worthless when I walk around London and have someone click their tongue at me and tell me to speed up.', '"Walk,Green,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', 'You make yourself do the physical aspects for a Christopher Nolan film!', '"Yourself,Film,Physical"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd56', '"The spirit of Dunkirk is something everyone grew up learning about. After Dunkirk, everyone came together and it set the tone in the U.K."', '"Learning,Together,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd57', '"I think Irish women are strong as horses, incredibly loyal and for the most part, funny, witty, bright and optimistic in the face of devastating reality."', '"Funny,Women,Reality"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd57', '"When I first came to Hollywood, I could not break into movies."', '"Movies,First,Hollywood"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd57', '"The image of Ireland is projected as a male image in the acting world, similar to the way that the word of Ireland is male dominated."', '"World,Way,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd57', '"I\'m Irish and always will be, but America has taught me so much. Maybe it\'s here in the U.S. that we find a healing, for in the broader melting pot we get to look at some of these self-destructive attributes that we bring to bear upon our own quarrels and begin to solve them in ways other than just splitting apart."', '"Look,Me,America"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd57', '"People think we are such great talkers, but there is so much silence in Ireland about certain issues."', '"Great,Silence,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd58', 'There is no Democratic or Republican way of cleaning the streets.', '"Way,Republican,Cleaning"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd58', 'It makes no difference if I burn my bridges behind me - I never retreat.', '"Me,Never,Burn"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5a', 'A democracy is a volcano which conceals the fiery materials of its own destruction. These will produce an eruption and carry desolation in their way.', '"Democracy,Way,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5a', '"No one ever became, or can become truly eloquent without being a reader of the Bible, and an admirer of the purity and sublimity of its language."', '"Bible,Language,Purity"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5a', '"The known propensity of a democracy is to licentiousness which the ambitious call, and the ignorant believe to be liberty."', '"Democracy,Believe,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5a', 'The gentleman puts me in mind of an old hen which persists in setting after her eggs are taken away.', '"Me,Mind,Gentleman"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"I have a bit of a traveling addiction, and, ah, yeah. I went to, ah, Bali this summer."', '"Summer,Addiction,Bali"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'I\'m really obsessed with the past.', '"Past,Really,Obsessed"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"But did I think it would last more than 13 episodes at the time? No, I didn\'t think that. I never know."', '"Time,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"I like people and get along, and I\'m afraid to express my anger and my rage."', '"Anger,People,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'The reason I took Early Edition - besides the fact that I liked it - was that it enabled me to start a production company in New York City. It\'s a low-budget film company to produce and direct movies.', '"Movies,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"But basically what I like are the possibilities, and the fantasy element of the show. Not science fantasy so much, but fantasy, the humanistic elements and how people relate when they\'re in a dire situation or comedic situation."', '"Science,People,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'I really wanted to be born a woman. It all started there. A South American woman. And I\'m upset that I was born a white Jewish male. I\'ve been angry since.', '"Angry,Woman,White"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'But I\'m trying to play into this role as much as possible and be a nicer person in real life.', '"Life,Real,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"You know, it\'s a very sexist society, Indonesia."', '"Society,Know,Sexist"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"It got a little boring I guess, playing the same note over and over."', '"Boring,Guess,Same"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"Well, I just wanted to be a person. I just wanted them to keep writing me as humanistic as possible."', '"Me,Person,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"But I like being nasty. I like being cranky. Especially if it\'s a cold day in Chicago, it\'s nice to just take it out on Kyle, because he\'s so easy to scream at, you know?"', '"Day,Know,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"I use that as my responsibility on the show, to be the pragmatist."', '"Responsibility,Use,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"Unfortunately, the public might not know that we get a script usually two days before shooting. So sometimes I\'m shooting an episode and don\'t even know how it\'s going to end because I haven\'t read that yet."', '"Sometimes,End,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"But I used to have a bit of a gambling problem. And that would have been the answer to my prayers. It got worse when I started playing this character, too."', '"Character,Gambling,Answer"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'I wanted to do an episode about Chuck having a gambling problem. I wanted to portray my addiction on the show. But I think it\'s a little edgy for Saturday night.', '"Night,Gambling,Addiction"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', '"No, but I\'m really lucky, because I\'m not the superhero."', '"Because,Lucky,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'And TV is not the easiest place to be dangerous or on the edge. Especially on a Saturday night.', '"Night,Place,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5b', 'I used to be more of a wild kid. But I\'ve slowed down.', '"Wild,Down,More"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Whatever I start living like and whatever I start going through in my life, that\'s how I\'m gonna be sounding. It might sound a little different if I get more comfortable."', '"Life,My Life,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I wouldn\'t say I was the best kid but I always had a good heart.', '"Best,Good,Heart"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I wanna say to anybody that\'s trying to come up and go viral, push forward. Don\'t stop. Don\'t wait for nobody. Do it yourself. Ask for help, but don\'t wait for help."', '"Yourself,Wait,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Whatever happens, happens because I\'m trying to dot every \'I\' and cross every \'T.\'"', '"Trying,Whatever,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I can\'t say, \'Damn, I want to sing like Beyonce.\' All I can do is sing like Fivio Foreign and pray to God that\'s good enough."', '"God,Good,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Even though I\'m laughing all the time, I\'m watching all the time. I was observant and I got to learn people easy like that. So, I learn people good."', '"Time,Good,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Even when I be telling people like I\'m only dropping one album, they be like, \'Nah, bro, you gotta keep going.\'"', '"Keep Going,People,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Me being a rapper takes up too much of my time. I can\'t really do the things I need to do, but I need the money."', '"Money,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I feel like if you do one album, you don\'t give people the chance to judge you twice. If they judge you once and that legacy goes on, you\'ll go viral."', '"Chance,Legacy,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I am intelligent, little do y\'all know."', '"I Am,Know,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"One album, one and done, I\'m outta here. I ain\'t tryna be rappin\' for mad long."', '"Long,Done,Mad"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I don\'t even feel like a rapper.', '"Feel,Like,Even"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I\'m an introvert.', 'Introvert', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I always gotta be doing something.', '"Doing,Always,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I really wanted, when I was a little, little kid, I wanted to collect rocks. I don\'t know why. I didn\'t know nothin\' about them. I just liked to pick them up and keep em."', '"Rocks,Know,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"Drake is a man of the art, so he appreciates the new sounds and new music. He\'s always in tune with the music and the story behind it."', '"Art,Music,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I want my music in movies.', '"Music,Movies,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', '"I\'m influenced by like, 50 Cent and Chief Keef \'cause they were rapping about the same things I was living."', '"Living,Things,Same"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I believe in astrology. I really go off of energy.', '"Believe,Energy,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'Viral don\'t mean I\'m outside wilding. I can go viral in the club or in the studio.', '"I Can,Go,Outside"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I have different goals. I want to sign artists. I want to open up businesses.', '"Goals,Open,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd5d', 'I need Grammys.', '"Need,Grammys"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Being beautiful isn\'t everything... Sometimes it\'s interesting to show how you feel on the inside on the outside, just through expressing yourself."', '"Beautiful,Yourself,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'Vulnerability is the strongest state to be in. How boring would it be if we were constantly dominant or constantly submissive?', '"Boring,Vulnerability,State"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m in so many videos. There was a period of about two years where I danced for everyone: Kylie Minogue, Ed Sheeran, Jessie J, Taio Cruz. It got to the point where my fees were double the other girls\', and I wouldn\'t even have to audition. They\'d call my agent directly and say, \'We want twigs to come in.\'"', '"Everyone,Two,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I want people to see what\'s inside my head rather than just looking at me.', '"Me,Looking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Sometimes I feel 15; other times, I feel fully grown and mature and handling all my business. It can waver from day to day, hour to hour."', '"Business,Day,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Fashion\'s important to me, but beauty fades. All that stuff is fun while it lasts, but anything can happen tomorrow. You\'ve got to have so much more about you than the way you look or your clothes."', '"Beauty,Tomorrow,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'ve soaked up so much through dancing, but I also have to be still. I want to be silent and read, to shut up and take time to respect the vision someone put into a book."', '"Respect,Time,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Twigs has been my nickname for years, and I guess a lot of people close to me called me Twigs, like, as a nickname. Before I even did dancing properly or anything, like, substantially creative, I was still Twigs."', '"Me,People,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"You have to recognize at some point that even though you have the passion and creative level to be able to do something, you might have to do a lot of prep. Sometimes you just can\'t do it as quickly as you want to do it."', '"Passion,Sometimes,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"When I first released music, and no one knew what I looked like, I would read comments like: \'I\'ve never heard anything like this before; it\'s not in a genre.\' And then my picture came out six months later: now she\'s an R&B singer."', '"Music,Picture,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I don\'t know if I\'m a tortured soul, but I was born heartbroken. I remember feeling it when I was so young. I was like, \'Mum, it hurts.\'"', '"Soul,Remember,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m not thirsty. I\'m not a pop star. I don\'t want to reign over all forever... I don\'t want to be famous! It makes me feel sick, the thought of being a famous person. It\'s just not me."', '"Famous,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I always felt like Tahliah\'s a very grown-up name to have. It\'s a pretty name when you\'re young, and then I think when I became a young lady, it felt kind of like a lot to grow into for some reason. I don\'t know. It sounds kind of regal. I never really liked it. I always felt like I couldn\'t live up to it."', '"Grow,Lady,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I was always the poor kid, even though I very much tried to pretend to be the other way. Always well presented. Always really active in the school, doing fashion shows, plays, involved in every single aspect of the school. Overcompensating, I think, for the fact that I knew I wouldn\'t be going on the ski trip every January."', '"Way,School,Poor"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I think we live in a culture where it is really difficult to get privacy because everything is so accessible. It\'s very difficult to maintain your comfortable life with a sort of mystique.', '"Life,Culture,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m a strange person - I don\'t really get rewards out of how many hits I have on YouTube. I love it, and I\'m grateful, and it\'s important to me. But does it equal peace within me? No, it doesn\'t."', '"Love,Peace,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Half of my life, I\'ve had people staring at me because they think I\'m funny-looking and ugly. The other half of my life, I\'ve had people staring at me because they think I\'m fascinating. Everything neutralises. It\'s more of a statement on society and how weird it is."', '"Life,Society,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I really enjoy the fun of putting something out and people liking it or hating it or talking about it, but vacuous attention, it feels disgusting. It\'s like a hangover."', '"Fun,People,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I was never the pretty girl at school. I\'m tiny and mixed-race. I grew up in a white area. I was always the loner.', '"White,School,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Textures apply to everything I do. Even within my music, I like smooth things, and then hard and fluffy things, all giving them their place to shine."', '"Music,Shine,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I once said to a boy, \'You\'re a really good kisser,\' and he said, \'You\'re only as good as the person you\'re kissing.\' I think it\'s the same with the music."', '"Good,Music,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"If you\'re an artist, you have to use everything to your advantage, even the pain."', '"Pain,Everything,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'ve never been into the typical R&B voice, with runs and bluesy sounding words. That doesn\'t suit me."', '"Me,Words,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Being a gal, people can be a bit patronizing. \'Oh, look at you using the computer.\' They would never say that to a boy. And I don\'t let them do it to me."', '"Look,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I don\'t know any Beatles songs. My dad never listened to Elvis or Sting or Bowie. Any band name that\'s on a t-shirt, I probably won\'t know their music, like AC/DC or whatever. I don\'t know what that is. As a kid, I would sing along to artists like Tania Maria."', '"Music,Dad,T-Shirt"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m appealing to people who want something different, but the world, on the whole, doesn\'t really embrace different things. Not on the whole."', '"World,People,Embrace"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"It\'s weird: for someone who mostly really exists online, I\'m actually not very interested in the Internet at all."', '"Internet,Weird,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"When I was younger, I had conversations with friends about wanting to create something different. Every young musician probably thinks that. But it\'s difficult to do, because there are only so many words, notes, melodies, songs. But as soon as I stopped thinking and started feeling, it worked. I didn\'t realize it till I was done."', '"Thinking,Words,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Obviously I know if you\'re putting yourself out there, saying, \'Hey! Listen to my music!,\' with pictures of yourself in the magazines, then people are going to judge you. \'I hate her music. I hate her hair. I hate her production. I hate her videos.\' Fine: don\'t care. That\'s the great thing about art: it\'s not for everyone."', '"Art,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m an artist, and I\'m a bit weird, and I\'m probably a bit eccentric."', '"Weird,Artist,Eccentric"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"It\'s really easy to project this whole ideology of what being an artiste is, and I\'m just not down with intellectualizing it. I just think, if you feel like doing something, then do it."', '"Feel,Doing,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"What makes me happy is having a really nice day out with my mum, or getting better at something I\'ve been working hard at."', '"Me,Day,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I love my music, so I want to produce, write, and serve my music. I\'ve had to learn about EQ frequencies and programming and space and clutter and how to be a better piano or bass player - everything."', '"Love,Space,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"Racism is unacceptable in the real world, and it\'s unacceptable online."', '"World,Real,Online"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I love things that are harsh and things that are too loud. And I love lulling people into a false sense of security. That\'s life.', '"Life,Love,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"When I first put out music, people didn\'t know what I looked like. They called it a new type of something; they couldn\'t put a genre on it - it was where indie and urban kind of meet in the middle. I thought that was quite exciting."', '"Music,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I definitely keep myself to myself; I don\'t really go out. If my friends want to see me, they know to come around to my house."', '"Myself,Me,See"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I moved to London to go to dance school when I was about 17, but then I realized that I didn\'t want to be a dancer anymore, so I dropped out after five or six weeks. All I wanted to do was sing and make music."', '"Music,Dance,School"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I feel confident that the work I\'ve put in will make people see me as a music artist before anything else.', '"Work,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I write exactly what I think. If it\'s a raw subject, I write lots of things and then pull out all the fluff words."', '"Words,Things,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', 'I\'m not going to become a costume version or caricature of myself; I like to morph.', '"Myself,Version,Caricature"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m a country girl. The more big cities I go to, the more fashionistas and designers I meet who want to dress me, the more I have all these kind of superficial but amazing experiences, the more I just realize that I\'m from Gloucestershire."', '"Amazing,Me,Dress"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"In school, I had a tough time fitting in, and dancing was my way of being in my own element. As a teenager, I became a bit disillusioned with it. Even with competitions, I\'d win, but still there would be tears."', '"Time,Tears,Tough"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I spent my whole teenage life trying to get to London and go to dance school, but when I got there, I couldn\'t wait to get to the clubs on weekends. I knew I wanted to make music."', '"Life,Music,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"A few years ago, I found out that there\'s a lot of Gypsy blood on my mother\'s side. I\'m wild in that way - I\'ve been brought up to do my own thing."', '"Way,Wild,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fcaf', '"I\'m the happiest when I\'m in the studio, not on a beauty parade."', '"Beauty,Happiest,Parade"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd61', '"I was myself brought up with my brother, whose name was Matthias, for he was my own brother, by both father and mother; and I made mighty proficiency in the improvements of my learning, and appeared to have both a great memory and understanding."', '"Learning,Great,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd61', '"Now Herod was an active man, and soon found proper materials for his active spirit to work upon."', '"Work,Man,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd61', '"Now, my father Matthias was not only eminent on account of is nobility, but had a higher commendation on account of his righteousness, and was in great reputation in Jerusalem, the greatest city we have."', '"Great,City,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd61', '"Yet did that Antiochus, who was also called Dionysius, become an origin of troubles again."', '"Origin,Who,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'The hype man\'s job is to get everybody out of their seats and on the dance floor to have a good time.', '"Time,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I\'ll tell you one thing you can\'t do: you can\'t put your shoes on, then your socks on."', '"Shoes,Your,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I wear my Viking helmet because the horns define how sharp my brains are. If you try to rub me the wrong way, I will stick you with both of my horns."', '"Me,Way,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Best advice that I ever got is to do whatever it takes to make myself happy, so that I\'ll be able to make others happy. If I\'m not happy, I can\'t make other people happy."', '"Best,Myself,Advice"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I grew up playing about 15 instruments and the way that I was able to accomplish that was by cutting my classes, hanging out in the band room all day, and going from one instrument to the next to the next, until I learned how to play everything by ear."', '"Day,Way,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I\'ve taken a lot of time to build up the name Flavor Flav, but this could come tumbling down in 30 seconds. If you want to keep what you worked for hard all your life, then you got to do the right thing in your life."', '"Life,Time,Do The Right Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"If anyone wants to know what the definition of \'dope\' means, it\'s: \'Definition of Public Enemy.\'"', '"Enemy,Know,Dope"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Definitely, I think I\'m a life coach for real. The lessons I give are lessons you can take to the bank."', '"Life,Real,Bank"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I look more to the future. That\'s where my head is at.', '"Future,Look,More"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"One thing you can\'t do with babies, you can\'t give them steak."', '"Steak,One Thing,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I remember rap music. We used to party and dance off of it. Today it\'s all about a whole different angle... Rappers are going against each other, and it\'s more of a bragging, boasting thing."', '"Music,Today,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"If I do look back, I\'ll say that I\'m blessed. I\'m blessed, and I appreciate God for not only letting me live through everything, but to prosper."', '"God,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Hip-hop is when you have crowd participation; when you chant at the audience and they chant back at you; when you wave your hands in the air like you just don\'t care; or some breakdancing. Everything today is just low-beat, real bass-y, bass-y, good rap records."', '"Good,Today,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I\'m trying to grow. I don\'t want to stay on the same page.', '"Grow,Trying,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"The moments we have behind us, you won\'t be able to see again. We\'re only responsible for what we live in right now."', '"Live,See,Behind"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I\'m not doing no more \'Flavor of Loves.\' I\'m trying to grow. I don\'t want to stay on the same page. You can\'t stay on the same page in order to get to the next chap.', '"Grow,Doing,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I set our house on fire when I was a little child playing with lighters. Boy, did I burn the place down!"', '"Fire,Place,Burn"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I ain\'t scared to do another dating show, but I ain\'t really trying to. I want to do a talk show or something. I\'ve done enough dating on television. I\'m ready to spread my wings, and go down other avenues."', '"Dating,Wings,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"My chicken ain\'t no joke. I ain\'t scared to go up against the Colonel, tastewise."', '"Chicken,Go,Scared"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Queen Latifah used to help me out with my kids, because while we were all out on tour - Public Enemy, Naughty By Nature, Queen Latifah, Heavy D - when Public Enemy went onstage, I didn\'t have anybody solid to watch my kids. So, Latifah would help me out."', '"Nature,Naughty,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Back in the day, cooking definitely was the thing where you could make a lot of money. Also, it was something that I liked to do."', '"Money,Cooking,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Back in the day, when the D.J. would be playing a record, I\'d be on the mic trying to hype up the crowd. So once Public Enemy became a rap group, I decided that that\'s the role that I wanted to take on. I wanted to be the one that was hyping, because I\'ve always been good at it. I can hype up any crowd."', '"Good,Day,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'Your man Flavor Flav is living!', '"Man,Living,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I have over a hundred clocks. I\'ve got fancy clocks and clocks from all over the world that people made for me.', '"Me,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"What I\'m trying to do is put back into rap music what\'s missing - which is the good part, the fun part, that party part."', '"Good,Music,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I got a way to get through to kids. I try to take that and use that to my advantage. If we work on the kids right now, I\'m telling you, they\'ll be making less mistakes, the jails will be gettin\' less full. It\'s all about what we do with the kids."', '"Work,Way,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I worked as a head cook at courthouses and high schools. I left it behind when I started getting into my music real heavy.', '"Music,Real,Behind"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"When I was in jail, I was a lot of people\'s favorite person. I practically ran the jail. I had more freedom than the police."', '"Freedom,Police,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'My parents owned a soul food diner. It inspired me to go to culinary school.', '"Food,Me,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I\'m a real big celebrity. I\'m this megastar.', '"Real,Big,Celebrity"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Honestly, Flav is not much of a video game player these days. BUT, I used to spend hours on Time Crisis. I beat all levels, man."', '"Time,Man,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I know I have a hit show on my hands.', '"Hands,Know,Show"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I try and spend a lot of time with my kids. I try and have fun with my kids. I try to put father time in there.', '"Time,Fun,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I got a lot happening, a whole lot, and it\'s not always easy being me."', '"Me,Always,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"We never broke up. As long as I\'m living and as long as Chuck D is living, Public Enemy is always going to be alive."', '"Long,Alive,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Doing scripted acting is a challenge to me. I can\'t remember things too good, so remembering lines is a challenge to your boy."', '"Good,Me,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'I got my degree in culinary arts in 1978.', '"Degree,Got,Culinary"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"I just want to show the world it\'s never too late to get your diploma, and show kids they should stay in school and not wait until you\'re old to get it."', '"Never Too Late,World,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', 'Remember the diner in \'Happy Days?\' I do want to do a show like that. But an updated version.', '"Remember,Happy,Version"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd62', '"Since 1987, when I got my first one, I\'ve been wearing a clock around my neck 24/7. You feel me? 24/7."', '"Me,Feel,Clock"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'Anything worth doing good takes a little chaos.', '"Good,Chaos,Doing Good"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"If you live a rebellious lifestyle, then you rebel against things because they go against your ideals and the integrity of who you are as a person."', '"Integrity,Lifestyle,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"It\'s so easy to fall into a comfortable groove in life where you do the things that you like, and because of that, often times, we don\'t grow or change because we\'re not pushing ourselves."', '"Life,Change,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"About 13-14 years ago, I went back to my alma mater, Fairfax High School, and ran into the music teacher. She invited me to come speak to the kids about the viability of a music career. When I went into the room where I used to play every day in a big orchestra, they had nothing!"', '"Teacher,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"A big part of my life is music education because it changed my life - but arts, academics and athletics should all be equally treated in the school."', '"Life,Education,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Later in high school, I met Hillel Slovak, who was the original guitar player of the Chili Peppers, and we became really close. We had a band, and we didn\'t like the bass player, so I started playing bass, and I got a bass two weeks later."', '"Guitar,School,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Turning 50 is a little bit of a \'taking stock\' moment. I feel probably a little dumber. I don\'t think I\'m as sharp as I was when I was younger, but I\'m definitely wiser and less likely to make gigantic blunders of an intellectual, spiritual, emotional or physical type."', '"Moment,Spiritual,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Music is like the genius of humankind, universal... People who have never really taken the time to get into music, their lives are a lot smaller. Kids deserve the richness and dimension of it in their lives."', '"Time,Music,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I have a trainer, a really nice woman named Nina Greenberg, and she got me a training plan, and we go running in the canyons in Malibu. It\'s just beautiful up there, absolutely gorgeous. You see bobcats up there sometimes."', '"Beautiful,Me,Training"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I grew up with all these old jazz guys in the \'70s in L.A., and they grew up idolizing Charlie Parker, Charles Mingus, Lester Young - all of these incredible musicians."', '"Jazz,Young,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"All I knew about Ethiopia was from a few records that I like, as well as what I read about the famine. But you get there and it\'s another world. It\'s filled with art and music and poetry and intellectuals and writers - all kinds of people."', '"Art,Music,Poetry"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"For me, music was the only reason I went to school. I was kind of a street kid, in a lot of trouble committing crimes and stuff. Music gave me something to focus on."', '"Music,Focus,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Steven Adler and I played football in the street when we were 12. I remember rehearsing in my bedroom with my first band, and some kid climbed over the fence of my backyard and peeked his head in the window to see who was rocking. It was Slash."', '"Football,Window,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"All my career, all that I\'ve really done has been based on emotion and intuition and gravitating toward what sounds good."', '"Good,Done,Intuition"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I just lucked into this weird, little obscure cameoesque film career. I just love being a part of film history."', '"Love,History,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I feel creatively vibrant. I have some great friends; I feel like I\'m capable of giving a lot to the world. And ultimately, that\'s what I really care about, is just giving."', '"Great,World,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"The most important thing to me with any politician is that they don\'t start wars, but education is a big part of that, too, because educated people are less likely to do stupid, violent things."', '"Education,Stupid,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"You teach your kids about your beliefs and tell them what you think is right and the conclusions that you\'ve come to from living in the world, and then they can make their own decisions."', '"World,Living,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I\'m at home, I just run all the time, you know; I get up, and I go pretty much four days a week outdoors. I go in the canyons around L.A., Malibu - just around L.A. there\'s a lot of different spots."', '"Time,Home,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Water is my main state. If I time before I run - like, to digest, like, a good hour and a half or so to digest, I\'ll eat oatmeal. but I\'m a vegetarian for the most part, so in general, I just eat grains and vegetables and fruit."', '"Time,Good,Fruit"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I studied chord theory and started playing the piano.', '"Piano,Playing,Theory"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I went to school and studied music for a year at USC, which unlocked a bunch of doors for me in terms of my relationship to music."', '"Relationship,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I was raised to think that rock was music for ignorant people who didn\'t think for themselves.', '"Music,People,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I feel like if we\'re not running, we\'re basically disrespecting our bodies. When you\'re running, you\'re really using your body for what it\'s meant to do."', '"Body,Feel,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I played trumpet in the school bands. I learned things I liked to play on my trumpet, but I didn\'t learn why this note goes with this note and why it produces that sound. Or how to create tension in the composition."', '"School,Create,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Ethiopia is such a great country, beautiful place."', '"Great,Beautiful,Beautiful Place"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I love entertaining people, I love playing music, and I love rocking like an animal. But at a certain point, you\'re playing gig after gig after gig, in town after town after town, and you\'re lying down, staring at another hotel-room ceiling, and it\'s like, \'I want to be home. I\'m a dad. I\'ve got kids.\'"', '"Love,Home,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"The Silverlake Conservatory is a nonprofit music school in Los Angeles where we teach music, mostly to kids, but to people of all ages - people who are old, people with beards, all kinds of people."', '"Music,People,School"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"My whole musical life has been an educational process, and I\'m just furthering my education and filling in the blanks. There\'s stuff that I want to know that I don\'t know."', '"Life,Education,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I worked full time jobs, basically doing manual labor until I could make enough money supporting myself as a musician."', '"Money,Time,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I started playing trumpet when I was 11 years old. All I wanted to be was a jazz trumpet player when I grew up.', '"Jazz,Old,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'We were these arty punks from Hollywood. I considered myself an intellectual.', '"Myself,Intellectual,Hollywood"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I was on a path that could\'ve really led to disaster, and the one thing for me that really kept me focused and gave me something to believe in and a sense of self-worth and a discipline was music."', '"Music,Path,Discipline"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"It\'s fun to just get out there and have a nice conversation when I\'m running. To be honest, when I do longer runs, the trail that I like to run up in Malibu has mountain lions, so I always feel I want to run with someone else."', '"Fun,Feel,Conversation"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When you make music, you\'re forming these invisible vibrations in the air into different shapes and consistencies and speeds in order to create music, and understanding how the math of that works just gives you more colors to paint with, and allows you to get to what you want quicker."', '"Music,Colors,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Being a dad and being in the Red Hot Chili Peppers and all the stuff I have to do... The trumpet requires a lot of diligence, and I haven\'t had the time."', '"Time,Dad,Hot"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"For me it\'s the high-water mark of American culture - not so much contemporary jazz, which has become kind of academic, but the jazz from the \'20s on through the \'70s."', '"Culture,Me,Jazz"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"The quality of instruction is very high at the Silverlake Conservatory of Music. It\'s not about being a rock star. It\'s about the fundamentals of music, theory and technique on a particular instrument, and playing in an ensemble or private setting."', '"Music,Quality,Rock Star"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I grew up being terrified of my parents, particularly my father figures."', '"Father,Parents,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I was a kid, and it was time to go to college, I thought, \'College is for people who don\'t have the street smarts to make it on their own - get in a band, get in a van, and get rockin\'."', '"Time,Street,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'The apparatus has to serve our improbability and improvisation. Being good and playing the songs is not enough.', '"Good,Enough,Serve"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"We were at the dark end of the L.A. punk scene, and that scene was full-on and violent and aggressive and wild and intense."', '"Aggressive,Wild,Dark"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"The last thing that should happen is funding cut for education; it should be increased. We need to put more money towards education, and anything else is abusive."', '"Education,Money,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I got with Nina Greenberg, I had been running for a few months already without a trainer. But then she gave me a program and guided me through my runs, showing me how to take care of myself and letting me know I should ice my legs and stretch - stuff I hadn\'t been doing."', '"Myself,Me,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I studied music at the most remedial level when I was a kid, through the Los Angeles public schools, with a little private instruction."', '"Music,Through,Level"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'Music is made up out of these building blocks. Studying how these blocks go together and what they consist of and the math of how it works - it\'s all the same stuff; it\'s just different aesthetics that we\'re talking about.', '"Music,Together,Building"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I was growing up, in L.A., I went to these schools, Fairfax High School, Bancroft Junior High School, and they had great music departments. I always played in the orchestra, the jazz band, the marching band."', '"Music,Great,Jazz"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Kids deserve arts, and it\'s just as important as science, math, history, English or athletics."', '"Science,History,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I did record a bunch of stuff, but the thing that usually stops me from doing that is that I\'m a terrible singer. I made a bunch of instrumental music, and it feels really good, but just as a singer, I\'m not good."', '"Good,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I always thought I was a pretty terrible actor.', '"Always,Pretty,Terrible"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I was in school, you could pick any instrument you want, and they\'d teach you how to play it. That changed my life. I loved playing music in school, and it sent me on my path as a musician."', '"Life,Music,Path"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Just so people know, the Silverlake Conservatory of Music is not at all about celebrity or fame or being a star. It\'s an academic music school."', '"Music,People,School"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"After running for a while, things really start to open up in your body. I felt like I\'d tapped into parts of my body that I hadn\'t before. I let things in the universe flow through me that opened me up in a really cool way."', '"Cool,Me,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Being a rock star isn\'t all it\'s cracked up to be, let me tell you."', '"Me,Rock Star,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I\'m always put in the unfortunate position of asking people to donate money and people I know in bands to play benefit concerts and all this stuff.', '"Money,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When I first heard about Twittering, I thought it was the most disgusting thing I\'d ever heard of in my life. It\'s like the devil: the idea that your personal life is there for everybody."', '"Life,Devil,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'Running opened up something beautiful in my life. I try to send the energy all over my body. I love the feeling of it.', '"Life,Love,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"As a musician I\'m about expressing what\'s inside, and I think everyone has a song in them that they need to get out, whatever their gig is."', '"Song,Everyone,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Music gave me something that was not only good for me - it gave me something to work on, something to be proud of and something that I really loved and have a love for - but also music was good for other people because you put joy into the world."', '"Love,Work,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"My father was out of my life when I was pretty young - when I was 7 years old, he was gone. I didn\'t see him for the rest of my childhood."', '"Life,Childhood,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I got my love of jazz from my stepfather, who was a jazz musician."', '"Love,Jazz,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When something comes up, and it\'s interesting, and I have the time, I\'ll do it."', '"Time,Interesting,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I wanted to play in a band, and I wanted to do music for a living, and that\'s what I dedicated my life to."', '"Life,Music,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'We always write way more than we put on a record. We always write a lot-lot.', '"Way,Always,More"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I like the idea of acting. Of all these things I\'ve done, sometimes I think I\'ve done well, and sometimes I think I didn\'t do well, but they are more cameos, and I come in and be crazy."', '"Crazy,Sometimes,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"With acting, I always feel conscious of what I\'m doing."', '"Feel,Acting,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Before every show, we get into a circle, hold hands, and someone makes a speech. Most bands are too cool for that."', '"Cool,Circle,Hands"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"We must improvise, and we must experiment, and we must do things that might go wrong, and everything we bring - the people and the equipment - must serve us in that goal."', '"People,Everything,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I love literature deeply. I view books as sacred things, and in writing my story, I\'m going to do my best to honor the form that has played such a huge part in shaping who I am."', '"Love,Best,View"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I love my life and my mistakes and my triumphs - all of it.', '"Life,Love,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I exercise; I have a big career. I\'m a parent, and I run a music school."', '"Music,Exercise,School"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'I\'ve always kind of been an in-the-moment kind of person. I don\'t think that far in advance or have any idea what\'s around the next corner.', '"Person,Always,Corner"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'Bands develop their own weird ways of doing things.', '"Weird,Doing,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Lucky enough, through the public school system, I had been able to have some music education, and that gave me something to focus on, and discipline - like a family to feel part of. There was a healthy family."', '"Education,Family,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"Outside of a couple of times I ran without eating right or being too tired, I always feel great after I run."', '"Great,Tired,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', 'Playing music is a beautiful thing. But listening to music is just as great.', '"Music,Great,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I\'m a performer and have managed to get my performing into the mainstream consciousness of the world, I guess."', '"World,Consciousness,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"I had a friend who had been teaching music for a long time, and he knew a bunch of teachers, so I just put up the money and started a school."', '"Money,Time,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd63', '"When Hillel died, it was during one of the happiest times of my life. I was married and completely in love and had a baby on the way."', '"Life,Love,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd64', 'Smoking is one of the leading causes of statistics.', '"Smoking,Statistics,Leading"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd64', 'It is now proved beyond doubt that smoking is one of the leading causes of statistics.', '"Smoking,Statistics,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd64', 'A decision is what a man makes when he can\'t find anybody to serve on a committee.', '"Man,Decision,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd64', 'Our forefathers made one mistake. What they should have fought for was representation without taxation.', '"Mistake,Without,Made"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd64', '"Statesmanship is harder than politics. Politics is the art of getting along with people, whereas statesmanship is the art of getting along with politicians."', '"Politics,Art,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"My mum is black, my dad is white, and when I was a teenager, people would say, \'So what are you? Are you black? Or white? What are you more of?\'"', '"Dad,Black,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I used to shop in ASDA all the time. Every now and then I still go in to get a little salad for lunch.', '"Time,Lunch,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I do loads of squats with weights. It\'s great for your bum and legs.', '"Great,Legs,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I hated my big hair. I always wore it straight.', '"Hair,Big,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'My album is very uplifting and positive and fun. That was my mission - to get people up on their feet and escape the seriousness of life.', '"Positive,Life,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"My mum is from Ghana, and she used to play highlife music in the house, and my dad used to listen to music."', '"Music,Dad,House"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I do body conditioning, spinning and yoga. On the treadmill, I\'ll do intervals of running flat and then on incline. I\'ll do that for an hour."', '"Body,Spinning,Treadmill"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"After my first video, I went out and had chicken noodle soup with my sister and manager. We were like, \'How rock n\' roll are we? Celebrating the first video with chicken soup.\'"', '"Chicken,Rock,Soup"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I normally hit the gym five times a week. I tend to do half an hour of cardio - on the treadmill or a spin class - then head for the weights. I do a lot of core work, obviously!"', '"Work,Cardio,Week"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I\'ve been hyper-conscious about staying away from rubbish. I don\'t eat white bread, white rice or cereal unless it\'s porridge."', '"White,Bread,Rice"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I\'ve worked in a call centre and as a nightclub waitress. I served champagne to Rihanna.', '"Champagne,Call,Nightclub"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I got to the point where I\'d featured on songs; I\'d done backing singing for major artists. I\'d done all these shows, but it was always for other people."', '"Singing,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I remember, one day, I just printed out about a hundred CVs, and I was running around London. I was going to modeling agencies, temping agencies, anything. I was so desperate."', '"Day,Remember,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I feel like I\'m quite versatile. I want to do lots of different styles.', '"Feel,Want,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"It\'s funny because the perception is that the typical \'X Factor\' contestant is the person who\'s just working 9 to 5 and just decides to one day go and audition. So yeah, for me, it was a very different story."', '"Funny,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I can\'t ignore what I grew up listening to. My parents used to listen to Michael Jackson non-stop. They used to listen to Luther Vandross, Lionel Richie, Stevie Wonder."', '"Parents,Listening,Ignore"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"There\'s so much pressure, but I think if you really love it, if you truly love it, and it\'s your passion to sing, then that\'s what will get through. I think if you don\'t have that, you\'ll realise quickly."', '"Love,Passion,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Even before I auditioned for \'X Factor\' the second time, I was doing a lot of dance music."', '"Time,Music,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I\'d love to write with some people from the U.K., like Ed Sheeran, Emeli Sande... there\'s a very long list."', '"Love,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Even writing verses from my first album, there were songs that I didn\'t use because I just felt that they weren\'t really for me. But I think that happens naturally when you write songs. You\'re in a different mood in every session. There\'s so many songs out there that could potentially be used by other artists."', '"Me,Mood,Happens"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I used to just sit in the living room and make up songs on the keyboard.', '"Living Room,Living,Room"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I used to hate performing in front of anybody, but I was forced to sing in front of family, at family gatherings. Then it slowly developed, and I started to love it."', '"Love,Family,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I\'m a believer in things happening for a reason.', '"Reason,Things,Believer"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Everyone assumes it is just \'Wendy who works at Tesco\' who goes to audition for \'X Factor,\' and then their lives are changed, wham, like that. Me, I am someone who has tried for years in the music industry."', '"Music,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Traditionally with debut albums, labels insist on a face, so people know who you are."', '"Face,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I didn\'t grow up in a wealthy family at all. Being at home all day and watching movies, that was a luxury."', '"Family,Home,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Before going on \'X Factor\' again, I felt like I\'d tried everything else."', '"Everything,Tried,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I\'d done an EP, and nothing came from that, and I didn\'t know where to go from there."', '"Nothing,Done,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I\'ve always loved working out. When I was little, my dad used to make me and my sister do 10 press-ups every day before we brushed our teeth in the morning. It was like a boot camp! Then I did a lot of athletics at school and was a dancer."', '"Morning,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I would never totally deny myself any specific type of food.', '"Food,Myself,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Just before I auditioned for \'The X Factor,\' there was nothing in my diary at all. I had no shows; nothing was happening. It was make-or-break time for me, and I had to consider doing another career altogether."', '"Time,Me,Diary"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"Everyone\'s path is really different, and you just have to be in the right place at the right time. \'The X Factor\' gave me that chance I needed, that platform."', '"Time,Chance,Path"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I\'ve waited so long to get to this point, and I\'m so happy to be making my first album. I want to be a performer and an entertainer."', '"Long,Happy,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', 'I\'d perform in the mirror; I\'d pretend to do interviews. I\'d practice my autograph for hours.', '"Mirror,Practice,Autograph"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"\'The X Factor\' was the final push I needed to have the presence and confidence on stage, which I didn\'t have before. It\'s a crash course in the music industry. If you can survive the show, you\'re ready for the industry."', '"Music,Confidence,Survive"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I put pressure on myself all the time. I felt it so much with \'Sax,\' but I had to just let go and enjoy it."', '"Time,Myself,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"The attitude among the people I knew was, \'Fleur wants to be a singer\' but it was never, \'Go for it. You can do it.\' Everyone was cynical because we\'d never seen anyone where we came from do it."', '"Attitude,You Can Do It,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd65', '"I uplift people and see the good in a bad situation. The worst is I\'m very critical of myself. If I do a performance, I watch it 100 times afterwards and pick it apart."', '"Good,Myself,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'You can\'t expect to hit the jackpot if you don\'t put a few nickels in the machine.', '"Motivational,Hit,Machine"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'The devil made me do it.', '"Devil,Me,Made"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"My happiest memory of childhood was my first birthday in reform school. This teacher took an interest in me. In fact, he gave me the first birthday presents I ever got: a box of Cracker Jacks and a can of ABC shoe polish."', '"Birthday,Teacher,Childhood"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'Violence is a tool of the ignorant.', '"Violence,Ignorant,Tool"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"If I could marry my motorcycle, I\'d roll her right up to the altar."', '"Motorcycle,Right,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'Funny is an attitude.', '"Attitude,Funny"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"When you\'re hot, you\'re hot; when you\'re not, you\'re not."', '"Hot,You"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'Get well cards have become so humorous that if you don\'t get sick you\'re missing half the fun.', '"Humor,Fun,Cards"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'The cost of living is going up and the chance of living is going down.', '"Chance,Living,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I\'ve had all that you could ask for. The fat lady has sung, and there\'s a standing ovation."', '"Fat,Lady,Standing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"Don\'t order one for the road, because the road is already laid out."', '"Road,Order,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I was number one in the ratings four times last year and twice this season. What could be more damn equal than that? If they get any more equal, I don\'t want it."', '"Damn,More,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I study a lot of philosophy. I want to be an example of how to enjoy this success, and that\'s exactly what I\'ve done. I\'ve enjoyed every moment."', '"Success,Moment,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"Everyone in this house and the houses next door knows when I\'m in the sauna because I start singing, and I sing the blues when I\'m in a really good mood. I have a really loud voice, you know."', '"Good,Good Mood,Mood"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'It\'s later than it\'s ever been.', '"Been,Later,Than"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I told CBS, \'My career is going down the toilet, and you\'re pulling the chain.\'"', '"Down,Toilet,Pulling"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"After having seen the job done on that first show of mine, I realized that I felt like I wanted to work again for a short while. Two, three years, then stop."', '"Work,Done,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"The secret of my success with Geraldine is that she\'s not a putdown of women. She\'s smart, she\'s trustful, she\'s loyal, she\'s sassy."', '"Success,Women,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I have the bug again. I\'m expecting the response to seeing the show again on Nick to be very good, and this will set the groundwork for what I want to do."', '"Good,Will,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I have my outlet for my humor through my characters, and I also have the intimacy of rapport with my fans that allows me to explain my philosophy and spirituality."', '"Humor,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"My main point is to be funny; if I can slip a message in there, fine."', '"Funny,I Can,Fine"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'Funny is not a color. Being black is only good from the time you get from the curtain to the microphone.', '"Funny,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'My show is my statement. What I have to say is on the screen. My life is my own. I don\'t want to talk about my private self. Why should I?', '"Life,My Life,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"A show hosted by a black had never been accepted, so the first time that knob\'s turned on, people are judging against all they have ever been taught. I may have been the first black in the house."', '"Time,Black,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"Most drag impersonations are a drag. But women can like Geraldine, men can like Geraldine, everyone can like Geraldine."', '"Women,Men,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"I accomplished what I set out to do. I wanted the whole cookie, and I got it. Now I want to spend more time with my children - make sure they don\'t go through what I did."', '"Time,Children,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'I tell fans who ask me why I\'m not doing comedy anymore that I\'m a different person. I\'ve grown and I\'ve matured. I\'ve made a transition to where I really want to be.', '"Me,Fans,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'It would be ridiculous for me to say anything negative regarding blacks having an equal opportunity on TV.', '"Opportunity,Me,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"Variety shows didn\'t disappear; it was the caliber of the artists, the classic vaudevillians that have passed on. They are gone, so there\'s a different caliber performer that\'s come along that hasn\'t had the time to work in the small clubs and get the experience."', '"Work,Experience,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', '"Things can be funny only when we are in fun. When we\'re \'dead earnest,\' humor is the only thing that is dead."', '"Funny,Humor,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd67', 'I think Mr. Wilson will have to be the rest of the way alone.', '"Alone,Rest,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I love to do something that\'s challenging to myself, and just to see the success, it makes me go harder and harder the next time."', '"Love,Success,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Being from Miami, you\'re used to the fact that your home is a vacation spot. But that\'s what makes Miami one of the best places in the world. We\'re so rich in different cultures, being so close to Haiti, Cuba, the Dominican Republic, and Puerto Rico, and then you\'ve got people who travel from all over the world just to come visit."', '"Best,Home,Travel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"My first love was basketball, but that wasn\'t gonna launch me, and I knew I had to get into other things. So me and my friends, we started making mix CDs and going down to South Beach or to the parking lot at Pitbull concerts to spend all night hustling."', '"Love,Night,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"If they can go out and buy my albums, I can at least make the sacrifice to holler at the few people who call. A lot of times I\'m busy so they\'ll get my voice mail. And if I can speak to them and I have time, I always text back. Because I think that\'s very important."', '"Time,Busy,Sacrifice"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'Hats off to T-Pain for the \'Low\' record.', '"Low,Hats,Record"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I wouldn\'t mind working with Outkast. I\'m a big fan of them.', '"Mind,Big,Big Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"You can go to some countries where people may not be able to conversate with you, but they can sing your lyrics word for word."', '"People,Go,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'It\'s always overwhelming when you come to another country and you\'re embraced in such a positive way.', '"Positive,Way,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I\'m influenced by all types of music.', '"Music,Types,Influenced"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"With my charity Big Dreams For Kids, I believe the more you give, the more you receive."', '"Dreams,Believe,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I\'m a huge fan of Taio Cruz. I\'m really liking what he\'s doing at the moment. I\'d love to do something with him.', '"Love,Moment,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I\'m just not sticking to one thing. I like to have fun with it. I like to spread myself in many ways, so you\'re gonna get all types of music."', '"Music,Myself,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I definitely want my fans to know that I\'m here to stay, and I\'m going to continue to give them hot music."', '"Music,Hot,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I\'m a perfectionist, and I\'m not going to let the world hear a record until it\'s ready."', '"World,Ready,Hear"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"The Florida sound would probably be best defined as heavy bass with high energy dance records. There\'s a strong Caribbean heritage in Florida which features a lot of uptempo music, and the music accents the sexy, body-oriented sound."', '"Best,Music,Sexy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I write all the time, even if it means recording in the hotel room. I write on the plane, anywhere, anytime I\'m inspired or have ideas."', '"Time,Hotel,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Music was definitely a way out. Instead of playing basketball, I was going to recording studios."', '"Music,Way,Recording"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'Giving is most important to show the less fortunate that you don\'t give up. You always want to live a better life.', '"Life,Better,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"At the end of the day I want to be the guy who experienced music in all type of ways, with hip-hop being the roots of it."', '"Music,End Of The Day,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I enjoy everywhere I\'m booked to go.', '"Go,Enjoy,Everywhere"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I\'m not the only one in the studio a lot of times, so I have my boys in there and they\'ll tell me and give me their suggestions and what they think."', '"Me,Tell,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I\'m always around people who want to drink very expensive champagne. But only when it\'s a celebration of success.', '"Success,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I love my fans, so when I get the chance to interact with them, it\'s beautiful."', '"Love,Chance,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I love the energy over here in the U.K., the hospitality is insane."', '"Love,Energy,Hospitality"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"The fans are always at the hotel waiting, they like to get pictures and autographs. I enjoy it all, the displays of love and support at the hotel and the shows."', '"Love,Waiting,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I\'ve always known, before I had a record deal, that the thing is to go out and put on the show. I\'ve been doing that from day one."', '"Day,Doing,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I like to take music from everywhere and put it in my style and let it be accepted.', '"Music,Style,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I went on tour with Beyonce before. I wouldn\'t mind doing something with her.', '"Mind,Doing,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"First and foremost, I\'m fans of the people I\'m collaborating with. And collaborations expand who you are."', '"People,Fans,First"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I enjoy putting out singles.', '"Enjoy,Out,Putting"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Growing up in Miami, having these different cultures and being inspired in so many ways musically has let me have a very long career, \'cause just when you think I\'m gonna do this type of record, I go and do something else."', '"Me,Long,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"If I get in the studio, it\'s very organic. I like to go off how I feel."', '"Feel,Organic,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I\'ve worked with so many different artists, and I\'m always willing to expand and do some new fun things as long as the music is fun and the fans appreciate it worldwide."', '"Music,Long,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"As a kid in the projects, I always looked forward to spring break. We\'d either have cousins visiting us for the week from up north, and we\'d all play sports together, or sometimes I\'d go to Vero Beach and hang with my cousins there."', '"Sports,Together,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"In my late teens and early 20s, I started selling mix CDs on the street."', '"Street,Late,Early"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Starting out with music, I was very successful, and me getting into film, I definitely look forward to giving it my all. What you put in is what you get out."', '"Music,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Growing up in my household with seven women, I\'d hear all types of music."', '"Women,Music,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"I think just growing up in Miami, there\'s gumbo of different cultures that influence us."', '"Influence,Us,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"When I found out that my mom was sneaking listening to my music, I decided to make sure that my music is very clean."', '"Music,Mom,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', 'I\'m a guy who just loves to reinvent myself.', '"Myself,Guy,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd68', '"Music is my life, and if I like a song, chances are the world will also."', '"Life,Music,World"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I had a general burnout: I got extremely tired; I couldn\'t do anything anymore. I canceled tours; I cancelled everything in my life. For a year and a half, I was completely sick; I couldn\'t do anything. So yeah, I wanted to write about it in my lyrics. \'Anatomy Of A Nervous Breakdown\' is really about that, the inspiration behind it."', '"Life,Tired,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"A good glass of red wine or maybe a little bit too much every now and then is just fine. Heavy boozing, not so much, because you don\'t recover enough from it."', '"Good,Glass,Red"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I might move to Finland, at least for a while, to learn the language a bit better, \'cause you don\'t learn any language better than in the country itself."', '"Better,Country,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"If you are waiting for this thing that might happen tomorrow, it probably will never happen. You need to activate it now! No one else is going to do it for you, and ten years are going to go by before you even know it."', '"Waiting,Tomorrow,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Living in Finland as a singer of Nightwish, I\'m used to having people around me all the time that know who I am. In the Netherlands, people never really knew or cared or whatever."', '"Time,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'It\'s good to reflect on life and take a step back and sit and relax and do something else.', '"Life,Good,Relax"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Unfortunately, life unfolds as it does, and you can\'t do everything at the same time, and you can\'t do some things if you can\'t spend the time."', '"Life,Time,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"When you used to be able to express yourself as an adult in your own language, or as I can do in English, for instance, it\'s sometimes hard to switch back to very simple talking, like I am forced to do in Finnish. So a real conversation, when I really wanna tell something, I can\'t do it in Finnish."', '"Simple,Yourself,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"The most metal? Some would say Slayer, but I think they\'re a dreadful band. Unbelievably boring. Terrible. Apparently it\'s not metal to say that, but it\'s a personal opinion."', '"Boring,Opinion,Metal"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"People think that when they come up to me, screaming things into my ear, that I will respond according to what they want. I\'ll turn around and smile and take the photo. But I\'m not somebody\'s marionette."', '"Smile,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"My Finnish is... I\'m sounding like a three-year-old, at my best. It\'s super hard to really have a conversation, unfortunately. I know a lot of words, and so reading signs and stuff is becoming better, or going to a supermarket. But some specific words, of course, you don\'t get in your first year."', '"Best,Words,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Now, when you\'ve been in the band for three years, you get used to the position, in a sense. I don\'t think about it every day like, \'Oh my God, I\'m the singer of Nightwish!\'"', '"God,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'You always speak the language you hear most.', '"Language,Speak,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'Both the guys in Nightwish and I have experiences with previous band breakups and all emotions that come with it. It\'s almost like dating.', '"Dating,Emotions,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Thinking Slayer\'s music is not my thing doesn\'t mean I don\'t respect the band for what they are and what they\'ve done. I just won\'t play it. As I can imagine they won\'t listen to mine either, for that matter."', '"Respect,Music,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Why should we bother making a super high-quality, expensive album if nobody is going to pay for it anyway and will just download it for free as an MP3 that has no depth whatsoever because of the small file size?"', '"Free,Will,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I joined a metal band with only guys when I was 17.', '"Metal,Band,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'Meeting fans and taking pictures is an extra I would like to offer when time and energy allow it. It\'s not something a fan can presume to have.', '"Time,Energy,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Making an album is always a puzzle: you start by seeing a lot of different pieces, and they all need to come together into one picture."', '"Together,Puzzle,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I don\'t need to be the singer of Nightwish 24/7 when I\'m not touring or when I want to go to the supermarket in my comfy pants.', '"Go,Need,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'We are all entitled to our own opinion.', '"Opinion,Own,Entitled"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I don\'t have a poker face at all - I have a very, very expressional face, and I have no control over that."', '"Face,Control,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I wasn\'t personally that familiar with the Classic Rock bands. That is where Jorn Viggo came in: he played me tons of that stuff - Deep Purple, Led Zeppelin, plus a lot of bands with cool songs, riffs, vocals, etc. We really listened to tons of music."', '"Cool,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I agree that it\'s a macho world, metal, but it\'s also a very, very social world, where people are loving music in respect for one another, female or male."', '"Respect,Music,World"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"When I have the opportunity to meet fans that support me, I always try to do so."', '"Opportunity,Me,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I think every physiotherapist will tell you that it\'s not a very good idea, and there are many musicians in the metal scene who have suffered severe damage - like, the guitar player from Iced Earth, Jon Schaffer, had severe neck problems due to headbanging."', '"Good,Guitar,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I cannot work on a Revamp album when I tour with Nightwish. And I cannot do any Nightwish stuff when I\'m touring with Revamp.', '"Work,Cannot,Album"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"There is a project that I did back in 2008 with a Norwegian guitar player, Jorn Viggo Lofstad, who plays in Pagan\'s Mind. We wrote a rock album, and we never released it."', '"Guitar,Mind,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I\'m not the kind of singer that\'s always super, super careful."', '"Always,Careful,Singer"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Arch Enemy is a female-fronted metal band, but so is Delain. They don\'t sound alike at all. The only thing they both are are metal bands, but the style within metal is so massively different that it doesn\'t really say much whether there\'s a girl singing or not. So it\'s really not so important."', '"Style,Singing,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'There seems to sometimes be an entire genre called \'female-fronted metal.\'', '"Sometimes,Metal,Genre"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"If I\'m happy, you can tell, and there\'s no way of faking it."', '"Way,Happy,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I had the idea to spend the year off in 2008 and start writing a rock album. I wanted to do something else other than melodic metal after more than ten years of After Forever. I thought it would be nice to sidestep into rock.', '"Start,Rock,Forever"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I didn\'t like progressive jazz or anything. Rock was something I like to listen to.', '"Jazz,Rock,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I always feel I need to do well regardless of the level of the band.', '"Feel,Always,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Who on earth would expect a band such as Nightwish, to give you, of all people, the phone call, \'Hey, can you come and join us now?\' Yeah, that turned everything upside down."', '"People,Phone Call,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Nightwish is my band, and so is Revamp. They both get my 100 percent, which is why I also cannot do them both at the same time. They\'re both my babies."', '"Time,Why,Band"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Actually, I consider both Nightwish and Revamp equal."', '"Equal,Both,Consider"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I don\'t always have to be the best. Things don\'t always have to be perfect.', '"Best,Perfect,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I really like to meet people, but only when I have the energy for it."', '"Energy,People,Meet"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"It\'s not so surprising that there are more women in metal bands. And they\'re not just fronting them. There are drummers and guitar players, bass players."', '"Women,Guitar,More"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Since the moment I joined with Nightwish, I have been working non-stop."', '"Moment,Non-Stop,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'Even though Nightwish is my life and I love what I do - I could do this every day - to not do it really makes you desire even more for it again.', '"Life,Love,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'Everybody needs to take a little distance from things.', '"Distance,Needs,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Make music when I want to in whatever style I would like to. That is something that I know that I\'m not the only Nightwish member who has that. That\'s a luxury we can take, and we will."', '"Music,Style,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Musically, I have little ambition. The only real ambition I have is to make music and do music whenever I feel like it, without any real ambition or planning."', '"Music,Ambition,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Revamp is a band that would deserve the hundred-percent devotion a band needs, and at this moment, I don\'t see any future for another band next to a band such as Nightwish, and with the ambition to become a mother, I will have to let Revamp go, which is a very sad decision."', '"Sad,Future,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"The success of Revamp is clear. We\'ve sold a lot of albums, we\'ve done very good tours, and wherever we play, we get a very positive response, and that\'s something that would be very nice to keep."', '"Positive,Success,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I\'m very happy with what I can bring into Nightwish, but I will probably want to keep on writing things. And that can take many forms as well."', '"Will,Happy,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"When After Forever stopped, I didn\'t want to first find a band, then see if I could write with them, figure that whole thing out, then record an album. Instead, I worked with people I knew would be good songwriters out of an idea how I thought it would sound like."', '"Good,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I\'m studying Finnish, and it\'s one of the five most difficult languages in the world. And the more I learn, the more I realize that\'s definitely true."', '"World,Difficult,True"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I have creative energy in me that needs to come out one way or another, but that\'s where Revamp comes in."', '"Me,Energy,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Sometimes, I would love to record a super-quiet album, but for some reason, I never really got to that because my heart lies with the heavy stuff."', '"Love,Heart,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I never really thought of myself as somebody to move abroad. It just came on my path.', '"Myself,Path,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I tried to learn the Finnish language, which is really, really, really hard, and I realized that if I want to really learn it, I need to move to Finland."', '"Language,Hard,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"My Finnish, it never really happened, but I\'m good in Swedish."', '"Good,Never,Happened"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I\'ve studied classical singing, but not to a great extent."', '"Great,Singing,Extent"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"For me, I\'m way more at home in heavy metal than I am in classical music."', '"Home,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I am a humble person.', '"Humble,I Am,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'But not to have music would be unnatural to me.', '"Music,Me,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'No... I don\'t like Slayer.', '"Like,Slayer"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I do know I will enjoy family life. What I\'ve seen from moms, or heard stories from people who became a parent, it\'s such a consuming thing; it\'s such a wonderful thing. I consider it an extreme luxury to have that time and to not have to do anything else, and just be with my kid."', '"Life,Family,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"Everybody meets a lot of idiots in their line of work, not just in music."', '"Work,Music,Idiots"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"The whole social media thing is ridiculous. Everybody gets to say what they want all the time. That\'s fine in theory, but it\'s not civilised. Imagine going into a bar, and everybody in that bar is talking like people do online. They\'d just get their teeth punched in."', '"Time,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"There\'s only so much planning you can do when it comes to pregnancies, y\'know."', '"Planning,Only,Much"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I have been fortunate enough to see many places of this earth and most certainly a lot of art, but I would be more interested to see more of the natural wonders of the world."', '"Art,World,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"I didn\'t think of my pregnancy as a handicap for one minute, but having said that, I think the only big challenge was being so tired all the time."', '"Time,Tired,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"When a pregnancy begins, those cells begin their mitosis, and during the first three months, everything from limbs to organs to the brain and neurological system is being developed, and I never realized that would consume so much energy: it drains every bit of energy you have, and your hormonal status is changed dramatically!"', '"Brain,Energy,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', '"To be honest, I deliberately tend not to post things like \'I\'m having a relationship\' or where I live. I\'m a bit reluctant to keep this kind of information up to date because people are inclined to see things like that as statements, and I rather keep a little bit of privacy, if possible at all."', '"Relationship,Information,Privacy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'Not everyone is as equally as adventurous as me. I get that.', '"Me,Everyone,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd69', 'I find the opera part in \'The Greatest Show on Earth\' challenging.', '"Earth,Find,Opera"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6a', '"Learning another language is not only learning different words for the same things, but learning another way to think about things."', '"Learning,Words,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6a', 'We have learned how to do a lot of things. We must try to relearn why.', '"Why,Try,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6a', '"Many, many, many small moves of many kinds can bring a way to manage change. The theory can come later."', '"Change,Way,Small"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6a', 'I consider that there are different degrees of civilization and there are many different ways of expressing it. But one is civilized or is not.', '"Civilization,Degrees,Expressing"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6a', '"Democracy may have arisen in the West as the way of striving for the universal aspiration to dignity and freedom, but it isn\'t alien to the underlying concepts that infuse religion and moral philosophy everywhere."', '"Freedom,Religion,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', '"The fact that the movement was carried on by women who, for the most part, had no money of their own and were totally inexperienced in organization, and that they won their fight in about two generations, makes a story often dramatic and always worth preserving."', '"Women,Money,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', '"You have had indeed a fair trial. It is a shocking thing when a judge of your high office is shown to have betrayed the truth and his honor, and I sentence you to the penitentiary."', '"Truth,Honor,Judge"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', '"It\'s so worth-while being a judge, because, if I make good, I can help prove that a woman\'s place is as much on the bench, in City Council, or in Congress, as in the home."', '"Good,Home,City"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', 'Each generation must recreate liberty for its own times.', '"Generation,Liberty,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', 'Whether or not we establish freedom rests with ourselves.', '"Freedom,Ourselves,Whether"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', 'The nature of the Catilinarian conspiracy was bad and bloody.', '"Nature,Bad,Conspiracy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', '"Owing to the fact that leaders in the women\'s groups made a point of serving on the jury here whenever they were called, we have always had an unusually high type of women represented on the jury."', '"Women,Always,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', 'You can hardly judge women\'s effect on politics merely from the action of individual women officeholders.', '"Politics,Women,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6b', 'It will take a long time for women\'s effect on politics to register so that we may properly appraise it.', '"Politics,Women,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6c', '"I enjoyed my time in the WRAF. There were plenty of people at the airfields where I worked, and they were all very good company."', '"Time,Good,Good Company"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6c', '"I met dozens of pilots and would go on dates. I had the opportunity to go up in one of the planes, but I was scared of flying."', '"Opportunity,Go,Scared"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"A muscle is like a car. If you want it to run well early in the morning, you have to warm it up."', '"Car,Morning,Fitness"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'Conventional is not for me. I like things that are uniquely Flo. I like being different.', '"Me,Being Different,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'When anyone tells me I can\'t do anything... I\'m just not listening any more.', '"Me,Listening,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I believe in the impossible because no one else does.', '"Believe,Impossible,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'People want to think that staying in shape costs a lot of money. They couldn\'t be more wrong. It doesn\'t cost anything to walk. And it\'s probably a lot cheaper to go to the corner store and buy vegetables than take a family out for fast food.', '"Family,Money,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I like being unconventional.', '"Like,Being,Unconventional"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"I love working with kids, talking with them and listening to them. I always encourage kids to reach beyond their dreams. Don\'t try to be like me. Be better than me."', '"Love,Dreams,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I don\'t always have the best eating habits. I like butter and ice cream. There are days when I should work out and I don\'t. But it\'s never too late to change old habits.', '"Change,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"I have been running since I was 7. I was trying to restructure the way my body was made instead of trying to master the way I ran. I would get so frustrated with my starts in practices that I would just cry. When I ran, I wouldn\'t even try to get out of the blocks, I would just run."', '"Body,Way,Cry"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"I was always doing something physical. My brothers and I used to have handstand contests. We\'d walk around the projects on our hands and see who could get the farthest. I was always playing football with them, basketball or racing in the street."', '"Football,Walk,Street"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I used to be teased for the way I wore my hair at school. I used to do things like wear a different-colored sock on each leg.', '"Hair,Way,School"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'The main reason I wanted to be successful was to get out of the ghetto. My parents helped direct my path.', '"Path,Parents,Ghetto"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I couldn\'t wait until I grew up. I used to look at my mom\'s stockings and put them on with her high heels and mess with my hair.', '"Mom,Look,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I don\'t do drugs. I never have taken any drugs. I don\'t believe in them.', '"Believe,Never,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"That\'s what I\'d like to do on the President\'s Council. Make sports and athletics available to every youth in America, not just one day a week like it was for me, but every day."', '"Sports,Youth,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"To do justice to a lifelong dream of being a writer, I must give it the intense concentration and focus I gave to track. To do both with excellence is not possible. It is with a sense of sadness and joyous anticipation that I leave track and move on."', '"Focus,Justice,Excellence"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', '"If you want to run as fast as the men, you\'ve got to train like the men."', '"Men,Fast,Train"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6d', 'I\'ve always overworked in the weight room. I love working with weights. I knew they\'d give me the strength I needed.', '"Love,Strength,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6e', '"Well, Warren Harding, I have got you the presidency. What are you going to do with it?"', '"Well,Going,Got"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6e', 'I have only one real hobby - my husband.', '"Real,Hobby,Husband"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'There is no age limit on the enjoyment of sex. It keeps getting better.', '"Age,Sex,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'My life has never been easy. It\'s like all the major events of my life have always been difficult.', '"Life,My Life,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I\'m a \'70s mom, and my daughter is a \'90s mom. I know a lot of women my age who are real computer freaks."', '"Women,Age,Computers"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I don\'t know that I would want to be married again, but I do love companionship."', '"Love,Know,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I frequently am contacted by people who want to thank me for \'The Brady Bunch.\' Whether they grew up during the show\'s original television run or are brand-new fans of the present generation, they tell me how important \'The Brady Bunch\' has been in their lives."', '"Me,Generation,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I don\'t remember ever not singing. My mother loved music, and she taught me songs, country music, spirituals. I would sing for people and pass the hat when I was 4."', '"Music,Me,Hat"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"When I first went to New York I was right out of high school, I was 17 years old, and I had never seen a building over two stories high."', '"New,School,Building"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'I started in live television and I\'ve done a lot of live TV and that\'s really the thing that I love best. I love flying by the seat of my pants.', '"Love,Best,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I still get so much fan mail addressed to Carol Brady, and I think a lot of it\'s through the Net. And I always answer it, if it\'s legible."', '"Always,Answer,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'I have four of the most incredible children. And I have five grandchildren.', '"Children,Four,Grandchildren"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"It was in 1969, and I thought, wow, you know, I really didn\'t want to do a TV series. You know, I had my own act, and I was performing in Vegas and doing all of these exciting things."', '"Know,Doing,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I don\'t ever remember not praying. Bedtime prayers, the rosary, praying for friends, relatives, for the sick and for those who had died. It was a natural part of our lives."', '"Remember,Relatives,Sick"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'My children and their happiness have always been my greatest concern.', '"Happiness,Children,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"Being a mom makes you far more compassionate. You have more empathy for people, more love. I was always taught to say thank you, and I\'m very grateful. And my kids have that quality, too."', '"Love,Mom,Empathy"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'I may have more than one friend with benefits. It\'s very healthy for the heart. I think no matter how old you are - and I am pretty up there in terms of numbers - I think you should do whatever makes you happy.', '"Heart,I Am,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', 'It\'s so important to keep moving and don\'t buy into the myth. I say do anything you feel like as long as you don\'t hurt yourself or hurt anyone else. And things don\'t stop working in your body or your mind.', '"Mind,Yourself,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"For me, \'The Brady Bunch\' is just a part of the fabric of my career, but for a lot of people, that\'s it."', '"Me,People,Fabric"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I do think children come in wired a certain way. Why else would I be filled with hope and optimism? You just could not keep me down for very long. You can call it grace or a gift from God, but I do think I came in with it."', '"God,Hope,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I had an instinct to gravitate towards people who were smarter than I was, teachers that were nice people that were trying to do things in life that were constructive, and that\'s what I gravitated to instead of what I saw and what I was in."', '"Life,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"You don\'t get happy by sitting around going on, \'Oh this is a horrible situation, what to do?\' You\'ve got to find the courage to change that. I think change is extremely hard for people."', '"Change,Courage,People"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"A lot of women say to me, \'You know, I really hated you because my kids wanted you to be their mother.\'"', '"Women,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"I grew up in a very large, poor family."', '"Family,Poor,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:46:00', '2023-05-29 11:46:00'),
	('393514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd6f', '"If you want to wear long hair or wear that dress, as long as you\'re not hurting yourself or anybody else, I say do it. If you want to go out and have a romantic, sexy affair, do it."', '"Romantic,Sexy,Dress"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"In order to be rated as good as a good man in the field of her earnings, she must show herself better than he. She must be more steady, or more trustworthy, or more skilled, or more cheap in order to have the same chance of employment."', '"Good,Chance,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"It is fatal for any body of workers to have forever hanging from the fringes of its skirts other bodies on a level just below its own; for that means continual pressure downward, additional difficulty to be overcome in the struggle to maintain reasonable rates of wages."', '"Struggle,Body,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"This position is untenable, and there can be no pause in the agitation for full political power and responsibility until these are granted to all the women of the nation."', '"Women,Power,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"Hence, within the space of two generations there has been a complete revolution in the attitude of the trades-unions toward the women working in their trades."', '"Attitude,Space,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"In the garment trades, on the other hand, the presence of a body of the disfranchised, of the weak and young, undoubtedly contributes to the economic weakness of these trades."', '"Body,Young,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"On the one hand, she is cut off from the protection awarded to her sisters abroad; on the other, she has no such power to defend her interests at the polls, as is the heritage of her brothers at home."', '"Home,Power,Heritage"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', 'The very fact that women now form about one-fifth of the employes in manufacture and commerce in this country has opened a vast field of industrial legislation directly affecting women as wage-earners.', '"Women,Country,Commerce"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', '"The workingmen have perceived that women are in the field of industry to stay; and they see, too, that there can not be two standards of work and wages for any trade without constant menace to the higher standard."', '"Work,Women,See"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd70', 'Their effort to place the women upon the same industrial level with themselves in order that all may pull together in the effort to maintain reasonable conditions of life.', '"Life,Women,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'True nostalgia is an ephemeral composition of disjointed memories.', '"Memories,True,Nostalgia"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Aging does not make women powerless objects of pity but colorful and entertaining individuals and, on occasion, fire-breathing dragons that wise people don\'t cross."', '"Women,Wise,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"In social matters, pointless conventions are not merely the bee sting of etiquette, but the snake bite of moral order."', '"Snake,Bee,Moral"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"In baseball, you can\'t tell the players without a scorecard, but in political commentary, you need a metaphor."', '"Political,Tell,Baseball"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"You can\'t pretend to be witty because wit is dry, subtle, lacerating, cynical, elitist, and risque - all impossible to fake. Humor, on the other hand, is broad, soothing, positive, inclusive, and smutty - to make sure everybody gets it. Pretending to be humorous is easy, and a great many people are doing it."', '"Positive,Humor,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"People are so busy dreaming the American Dream, fantasizing about what they could be or have a right to be, that they\'re all asleep at the switch. Consequently we are living in the Age of Human Error."', '"Dreams,Age,Busy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Time has lost all meaning in that nightmare alley of the Western world known as the American mind.', '"Time,World,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Whenever people are confronted by a prediction for the future that they simply cannot or will not believe, they always say, \'It will never happen in my lifetime.\' If the prediction is something they deplore and fear, they say it with calculated bravado, often adding a smug, snorty hhrrummph."', '"Future,Fear,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Optimists don\'t mind if you eavesdrop on them. They welcome it, in fact, because it helps them spread their fiendish gospel."', '"Welcome,Mind,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"I believe in a Republic of Merit in which water is allowed to find its own level, where voters, like drivers, are tested before being turned loose."', '"Water,Believe,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"To achieve the very pinnacle of good taste, the neoclassicists wrote their plays entirely in alexandrine verse, a rarefied meter that is uniquely tailored to the French language and fits no other."', '"Good,Language,Achieve"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Writers who have nothing to say always strain for metaphors to say it in.', '"Nothing,Always,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'The long march of Western civilization from pantheons of gods for every taste to one God for all has been thrown into reverse by celebrity worship to give us a plethora of ancient deities to follow.', '"God,Long,Celebrity"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"He travels fastest who travels alone, and that goes double for she. Real feminism is spinsterhood."', '"Alone,Real,She"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'I\'d rather rot on my own floor than be found by a bunch of bingo players in a nursing home.', '"Home,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Now the only thing I miss about sex is the cigarette afterward. Next to the first one in the morning, it\'s the best one of all. It tasted so good that even if I had been frigid I would have pretended otherwise just to be able to smoke it."', '"Best,Good,Morning"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"The witty woman is a tragic figure in American life. Wit destroys eroticism and eroticism destroys wit, so women must choose between taking lovers and taking no prisoners."', '"Life,Women,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Until feminists started wailing about the female\'s passivity, submissiveness, and something called \'victim status,\' I had no idea women were such doormats. My childhood was populated by Eleanor Roosevelt, Amelia Earhart, Pearl Buck, Marie Curie, Clare Boothe Luce, and the Duchess of Windsor."', '"Women,Childhood,Victim"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'American couples have gone to such lengths to avoid the interference of in-laws that they have to pay marriage counselors to interfere between them.', '"Marriage,In-Laws,American"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"I don\'t suffer fools, and I like to see fools suffer."', '"See,Fools,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Feminists, I hasten to add, are not all bad. In fact, they are an ideal bellwether, an invaluable aid in helping me form opinions on issues that I don\'t have time to keep up with. If the feminists are for it, I\'m against it; if the feminists are against it, I\'m for it."', '"Time,Me,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"If the West Point class of 1915 is called \'the class the stars fell on\' for the number of World War II generals it produced, my junior-high class of 1950 is the class a ton of bricks fell on from Hollywood\'s gut-wrenching portrayals of mother-love in \'40s-era movies."', '"War,Movies,Stars"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"If last words are to be audible and coherent, they need to be delivered before you have any tubes up your nose or down your throat. Otherwise, the nurse gets the last word when she says, \'Don\'t try to talk, honey.\'"', '"Words,Honey,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Democracy elevates by turning ordinary people into extraordinary ordinary people called celebrities.', '"Democracy,People,Extraordinary"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Showing up at school already able to read is like showing up at the undertaker\'s already embalmed: people start worrying about being put out of their jobs.', '"People,Start,School"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Americans worship creativity the way they worship physical beauty - as a way of enjoying elitism without guilt: God did it.', '"Beauty,God,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Writers, not psychiatrists, are the true interpreters of the human mind and heart, and we have been at it for a very long time."', '"Time,Heart,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'A man should never apologize!', '"Man,Never,Apologize"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Any woman who has ever worked in a gutsy male environment knows that the correct response to a randy remark is an even more salacious retort. But timid feminists don\'t see it that way. To them, the proper reply is a lawsuit - that safe, modern version of the old slap in the face."', '"Face,Woman,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Women\'s writing was coming along fine until feminists came along and turned it into Women\'s Lit.', '"Women,Coming,Fine"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Until the mid-seventies, the traditional or classic lesbian was always a spinster and often a tweedy intellectual, with a stark glamour that titillated men and women alike. This is the woman that feminists destroyed when they pressured the media for \'positive images\' of lesbians."', '"Positive,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Christopher Hitchens and I were not friends or even acquaintances. We never met or spoke on the phone, just exchanged occasional brief letters - notes, really - hand-written and snail-mailed at first, e-mailed later."', '"Never,Phone,First"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"In \'Cat on a Hot Tin Roof,\' I couldn\'t take my eyes off Judith Anderson as Big Mama."', '"Eyes,Hot,Mama"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"They don\'t call him \'No Drama Obama\' for nothing. He\'s even worse than we thought because he has committed the ultimate American crime, worse than anything he has been accused of so far: He has no sense of humor."', '"Humor,No Sense,Drama"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"I\'ve done pretty well as a professional fed-up. The tools of my trade so far have been irony, tongue-in-cheek mockery, and supercilious contempt, but these are highly civilized weapons designed for 18th-century French salons."', '"Done,Professional,Tools"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"Let\'s face it: \'Threatening\' people are the only interesting people around. The unthreatening are, by and large, competent mediocrities who take lemming-like aim at careers in television."', '"Face,Aim,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', '"To me, the thing that has always ruined Jane Fonda is her voice."', '"Me,Voice,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'We are incapable of leaving anything to the imagination and loath to leave anything out. Maniacal thoroughness has become our national verbal ideal.', '"Imagination,Anything,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd71', 'Some last words seem flat-out unbelievable.', '"Words,Last,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'I attribute my success to this - I never gave or took any excuse.', '"Motivational,Success,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Live your life while you have it. Life is a splendid gift. There is nothing small in it. Far the greatest things grow by God\'s law out of the smallest. But to live your life, you must discipline it."', '"Life,God,Discipline"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'I think one\'s feelings waste themselves in words; they ought all to be distilled into actions which bring results.', '"Words,Feelings,Results"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"A hundred struggle and drown in the breakers. One discovers the new world. But rather, ten times rather, die in the surf, heralding the way to that new world, than stand idly on the shore."', '"Struggle,World,Die"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'How very little can be done under the spirit of fear.', '"Fear,Done,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'Women have no sympathy and my experience of women is almost as large as Europe.', '"Experience,Women,Sympathy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"So never lose an opportunity of urging a practical beginning, however small, for it is wonderful how often in such matters the mustard-seed germinates and roots itself."', '"Opportunity,Lose,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"The martyr sacrifices themselves entirely in vain. Or rather not in vain; for they make the selfish more selfish, the lazy more lazy, the narrow narrower."', '"Selfish,Lazy,Martyr"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Were there none who were discontented with what they have, the world would never reach anything better."', '"World,Better,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'The most important practical lesson that can be given to nurses is to teach them what to observe - how to observe - what symptoms indicate improvement - what the reverse - which are of importance - which are of none - which are the evidence of neglect - and of what kind of neglect.', '"Improvement,Important,Lesson"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'It may seem a strange principle to enunciate as the very first requirement in a hospital that it should do the sick no harm.', '"Hospital,Strange,Sick"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'The greatest heroes are those who do their duty in the daily grind of domestic affairs whilst the world whirls as a maddening dreidel.', '"Daily,World,Duty"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'God spoke to me and called me to His Service. What form this service was to take the voice did not say.', '"God,Me,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'Wise and humane management of the patient is the best safeguard against infection.', '"Best,Wise,Management"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'The world is put back by the death of every one who has to sacrifice the development of his or her peculiar gifts to conventionality.', '"Death,Sacrifice,World"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Every nurse ought to be careful to wash her hands very frequently during the day. If her face, too, so much the better."', '"Face,Day,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"If a patient is cold, if a patient is feverish, if a patient is faint, if he is sick after taking food, if he has a bed-sore, it is generally the fault not of the disease, but of the nursing."', '"Food,Fault,Disease"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"If I could give you information of my life, it would be to show how a woman of very ordinary ability has been led by God in strange and unaccustomed paths to do In His service what He has done in her. And if I could tell you all, you would see how God has done all, and I nothing."', '"Life,God,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"She said the object and color in the materials around us actually have a physical effect on us, on how we feel."', '"Feel,She,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"A dark house is always an unhealthy house, always an ill-aired house, always a dirty house. Want of light stops growth and promotes scrofula, rickets, etc., among the children. People lose their health in a dark house, and if they get ill, they cannot get well again in it."', '"Health,Growth,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'I have lived and slept in the same bed with English countesses and Prussian farm women... no woman has excited passions among women more than I have.', '"Women,Woman,Bed"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Sick children, if not too shy to speak, will always express this wish. They invariably prefer a story to be told to them, rather than read to them."', '"Children,Shy,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Never speak to an invalid from behind, nor from the door, nor from any distance from him, nor when he is doing anything. The official politeness of servants in these things is so grateful to invalids, that many prefer, without knowing why, having none but servants about them."', '"Grateful,Door,Politeness"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"The very elements of what constitutes good nursing are as little understood for the well as for the sick. The same laws of health or of nursing, for they are in reality the same, obtain among the well as among the sick."', '"Health,Good,Reality"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Why do people sit up so late, or, more rarely, get up so early? Not because the day is not long enough, but because they have no time in the day to themselves."', '"Time,Long,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Badly constructed houses do for the healthy what badly constructed hospitals do for the sick. Once insure that the air in a house is stagnant, and sickness is certain to follow."', '"Sickness,Air,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"Everything you do in a patient\'s room, after he is \'put up\' for the night, increases tenfold the risk of his having a bad night. But, if you rouse him up after he has fallen asleep, you do not risk - you secure him a bad night."', '"Night,Bad,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', '"I have learned to know God. I have recast my social belief... All my admirers are married; most of my friends are dead; and I stand with all the world before me, where to choose a path to make in it."', '"God,Path,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd72', 'Do not meet or overtake a patient who is moving about in order to speak to him or to give him any message or letter. You might just as well give him a box on the ear. I have seen a patient fall flat on the ground who was standing when his nurse came into the room.', '"Speak,Moving,Fall"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I wanted to go to drama school, but when I got the part in \'Falling,\' I got an agent, so it seemed a good idea to work. I always did a lot of singing and dancing, so I am glad it worked out that way. I would like to study stage acting at some point, though."', '"Work,Good,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"\'The Silence of the Lambs\' is my favourite book, favourite film."', '"Silence,Film,Book"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"The Kate Winslet thing has been a shocker. I was like, that is the most ridiculous claim. Amazing, obviously. She\'s been my idol since I re-enacted \'Titanic\' and fell in love with Leo. And it\'s a privilege to be called the next anything. But I suppose to be the next you is all you can do."', '"Love,Amazing,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Why shouldn\'t there be more epic, brilliant female characters onscreen?"', '"Why,More,Brilliant"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I hope to create characters that people want to watch - and they either want to be or are, or it\'s something that they recognize."', '"Hope,People,Create"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'My characters do have some fantastic taste in men.', '"Men,Taste,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"In order for us to appreciate this world, we have to be a bit more honest, and I hope I do that."', '"Hope,World,More"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"In \'Fighting With My Family,\' there\'s a scene where I have to wrestle; I have to do the famous fight between Paige and AJ Lee. We actually did perform it in front of all those thousands of people. And just beforehand, we had a little dress rehearsal, and there were all these famous wrestlers going around and watching as well. Terrifying."', '"Family,Famous,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I wrestled at the Staples Centre at \'Monday Night Raw\' when I was 21 years old.', '"Night,Old,Monday"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I don\'t think I\'m going to be an international sex symbol. I mean, I know I\'m not going to be an international sex symbol."', '"Sex,Know,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"During the Me Too breakthrough, I was hanging out with Emma Thompson and Emily Watson - two people I\'ve looked up to my entire life. Talking to those women was so empowering."', '"Life,Women,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"For me, it\'s always been so obvious that the less we can edit our lives and more we show how normal we all are, the better."', '"Me,Better,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"We\'re learning things every decade we grow through, and ultimately, you do end up with a different way of looking at things."', '"Learning,Grow,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I think there\'s always some good reason to try and modernize most period things, because at the end of the day, they may have, I suppose, used a different language or a different etiquette, but ultimately, these are still people that loved and breathed and lived and ate and weed and pooed just like we do now."', '"Good,End Of The Day,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'We tend to kind of write women out of history.', '"History,Women,Out"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I remember being about six years old, for the first day of school, and sitting in the back of a Chrysler, pretending to cry while listening to Tracy Chapman."', '"Day,Remember,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"The biggest thing about \'Lady Macbeth\' is the fact that people are so surprised that this woman is so amazing, and really, it shouldn\'t be so amazing that this incredible character is on our screens."', '"Amazing,Character,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"That, for me, actually is the most important thing about doing a period film is trying to make these people as lovable as they are back then."', '"Me,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'My dad still collects newspaper clippings about me.', '"Dad,Me,Newspaper"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"If you ever want to be interrogated, get Michael Shannon to do it. He\'s an amazing man. I loved working with him."', '"Amazing,Man,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"For me, I really appreciate seeing real bodies on screen, that variation, not the same frames we saw for the majority of our upbringing, making us feel like we have to look that way."', '"Look,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"If you look at it, the corset is a very beautiful item, but when I put one on, I realized how little you could actually move. And I\'m a very physical person: I talk with my hands. And I felt how the clothes took that away from me. And that was the idea, I think. It was a way of limiting women."', '"Women,Beautiful,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I really take my hat off to anybody that steps in the ring because it\'s so hard - you\'re competing against your friends, and you\'re working in front of an audience who tells you exactly what they\'re thinking."', '"Thinking,Hat,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I think you\'re always attracted by characters that are a little bit like you, or at least the worst parts of you that you can finally accept and say, \'All right, at least I know that now!\'"', '"Accept,Worst,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"When I look for roles, I am looking for incredibly powerful women."', '"Women,Look,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"There\'s always going to be pressure, and there\'s always going to be an area where you disappoint. As a storyteller, you have to understand that."', '"Pressure,Always,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"There was one moment when I was in L.A., and he was teaching me a move. I just looked at him, thinking, \'Oh my God, I\'m being taught to wrestle by Dwayne Johnson. What the hell?\'"', '"God,Moment,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"The one thing that I always try and take with me, if there\'s, like, a remake, or you\'re doing something again, is that every generation has a new story to tell."', '"Me,New,Generation"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I grew up in a very loud and dramatic household, and we loved being in the spotlight."', '"Loved,Dramatic,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'Wearing a corset is extremely uncomfortable.', '"Uncomfortable,Corset,Wearing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'It\'s always shocking when you see a modern woman in a period story line. It doesn\'t make sense.', '"Woman,See,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I think it\'s so interesting which ways your career can go. I would have been a completely different actor doing a completely different story, and I would have missed \'Lady Macbeth.\'"', '"Lady,Doing,Story"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'The women I\'m attracted to playing I hope will mean something to someone.', '"Hope,Women,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Sometimes in the real world, there is fire between people."', '"Fire,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I love watching faces as they grow up. It\'s the difference between so many strong British actresses compared to what America does to women. I like a face that hasn\'t been tampered with.', '"Love,Women,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"There\'s a reason why there\'s a problem with bodies, and it\'s because you never actually get to see any normal versions of them."', '"See,Never,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I am learning on every job I do. There is something new every time.', '"Time,Learning,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I have been enormously lucky. My first role was in a great film by a woman director.', '"Great,Woman,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I have learned how to wrestle. You end up battered and blue - but so happy.', '"Blue,I Have Learned,End"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I know that my way of tackling a character is very different.', '"Character,Way,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I\'ve tried not to get too bogged down by what people want you to be.', '"People,Down,Tried"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Something that I\'ve always been really keen on representing is some honesty with the way that we view ourselves. That\'s something I\'ve always appreciated watching actors that I\'ve looked up to, is when they look like you and me, or they have a funny elbow, or they have, you know, a hairy face."', '"Funny,Honesty,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I\'m a bit of a gypsy. I live everywhere; I live out of a bag.', '"Bag,Live,Gypsy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"The whole wrestling art, it\'s a whole form, is performance, and that\'s what makes it so exciting to do."', '"Art,Performance,Exciting"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"If I can make my mark just a little bit, then great."', '"Great,I Can,Little Bit"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I can\'t remember a Friday when I was younger when I wasn\'t eating a pizza, flirting with the barman."', '"Remember,Eating,Pizza"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Every time \'Lady Macbeth\' and everyone involved in the film gets nominated, it\'s amazing."', '"Time,Amazing,Lady"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I grew up in a very loud family where you had to fight to get your voice heard, in a good way."', '"Family,Good,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"You are hugely responsible for people following you. You need to work out why you are posting, what the message is, and what you are doing to these people."', '"Work,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I think it\'s good to not edit your life too much, or you give people different standards."', '"Life,Good,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I was acting with all my childhood heroes: Meryl Streep, Saoirse Ronan, all of those amazing women."', '"Women,Amazing,Childhood"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I don\'t want to feel like I have to change myself or my image.', '"Change,Myself,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"What I\'ve noticed about Hollywood is, if you go out there shouting about who you are, they will love you for it. But if you go out not knowing what it is that you\'re representing, and you are just a canvas, they will make you into the thing they need you to be."', '"Love,Canvas,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"What we don\'t realise when we watch a normal film is how many times someone has run in just before a shot quickly to wipe away that sweaty moustache. You never see a normal spot, a bag under the eye or an unplucked eyebrow, because that\'s not how Hollywood works."', '"Bag,See,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"As beautiful as cinema is, it\'s a massive part of the problem of why we look at ourselves in the way we do."', '"Beautiful,Look,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Playing Paige, I felt I had to train to wrestle."', '"Train,Playing,Felt"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I like a role where some of the character\'s motivations are confusing or at least interesting.', '"Character,Confusing,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"\'The Falling\' was a big, flashy, bizarre experience. I kept on saying at the time it was a fluke because I did the audition, and I didn\'t think anything would come of it."', '"Experience,Time,Falling"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '\'Lady Macbeth\' is a great opportunity for me to prove that maybe the outcome of \'The Falling\' was not necessarily a fluke.', '"Great,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I can definitely hold my hands up and say wrestling wasn\'t something that I grew up watching.', '"Hands,Watching,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Why aren\'t there these epic roles for women, for whatever age you are?"', '"Women,Age,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'What\'s important is to listen before you react.', '"Important,React,Listen"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"If people are noticing the hard work I\'m doing, then that\'s a wonderful thing."', '"Work,Hard Work,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'Feisty women are my calling!', '"Women,Calling,Feisty"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I love all of Kate Winslet\'s characters. And Natalie Portman. If I can have a smidgen of what they\'ve done, that would be awesome."', '"Love,Done,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Throughout my life, I\'ve been that annoying kid on every stage at school, in every talent contest."', '"Life,Talent,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I do like a bit of danger. Guns, cars, running, bullets. I\'m up for it."', '"Danger,Guns,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Girls have that wonderful thing where they try to throw each other off, not wanting to appear too eager."', '"Try,Wonderful,Wanting"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I\'ve been told to be skinny before - it\'s already happened, but it\'s up to you to either listen or say no. I\'m not listening."', '"Listening,Skinny,Happened"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I used to reenact \'Titanic\' all the time.', '"Time,Used,Titanic"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'The fact that I\'ve been nominated for a BAFTA is insane.', '"Insane,Nominated,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I found out I got \'The Little Drummer Girl\' and my BAFTA nomination in quick succession, and I just didn\'t expect it to be like that. I thought there would be a lot more time in between. It\'s been an overwhelming experience."', '"Experience,Time,Drummer"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I think everyone\'s always interested in playing a spy, right? That\'s something we grow up admiring, which is so strange, but it\'s just a very clever and quick world that we all want to be a part of."', '"World,Grow,Clever"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Someone asked if I wanted to be the first female Bond, and I was saying that I don\'t think we necessarily need that whole conversation."', '"Bond,Conversation,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'Do we need to have a female Bond? Couldn\'t we just make something new?', '"Bond,New,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"As an actor, it\'s very interesting to make the audience love you while you are doing horrendous things."', '"Love,Doing,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I played Mary at the age of seven in my first nativity play, and I loved it - there is something so fascinating about embodying someone else."', '"Age,Someone,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"Everybody\'s story of getting into the industry is just as difficult as the next person. Whether you come from money or no money, it\'s not easy... you have to offer yourself; you can\'t expect someone to get you."', '"Money,Yourself,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"With \'Lady Macbeth,\' I had two other things offered to me, and they would have also been very fun, but you just have to figure that out. And then you do it."', '"Me,Fun,Lady"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I got a really good insight into the world of wrestling.', '"Good,World,Insight"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I always hate it when I see the wrong person in massive roles, so for me, my biggest fear would be accepting a role I thought I wouldn\'t find the rhythm of."', '"Fear,Hate,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"What audiences love with series is that they can invest in characters for such a long period of time, and it\'s the same for actors. You can truly tell your story; then it\'s done."', '"Love,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', 'I love Le Carre\'s writing.', '"Love,Writing,I Love"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"When you\'re given a platform, and you\'re allowed to perform, and someone\'s there to heighten you as opposed to dampen you, that\'s a nice feeling."', '"Someone,Nice,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd73', '"I want women on-screen that we all either want to be, or we know, or we recognize."', '"Women,Know,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', '"The game of life is a game of boomerangs. Our thoughts, deeds and words return to us sooner or later with astounding accuracy."', '"Life,Communication,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', 'Giving opens the way for receiving.', '"Wisdom,Way,Giving"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', '"Every great work, every big accomplishment, has been brought into manifestation through holding to the vision, and often just before the big achievement, comes apparent failure and discouragement."', '"Work,Failure,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', '"You will be a failure, until you impress the subconscious with the conviction you are a success. This is done by making an affirmation which \'clicks.\'"', '"Success,Failure,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', 'There is a supply for every demand.', '"Demand,Every,Supply"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', 'Hope looks forward. Faith knows it has already received and acts accordingly.', '"Faith,Hope,Looks"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', '"Intuition is a spiritual faculty and does not explain, but simply points the way."', '"Spiritual,Way,Intuition"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd74', 'No man is a success in business unless he loves his work.', '"Success,Work,Business"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I like the idea of taking off like a bird.', '"Bird,Like,Off"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When you\'re heartbroken, you\'re at your most creative - you have to channel all your energies into something else to not think about it. Contentment is a creativity killer, but don\'t worry - I\'m very capable of making myself discontented."', '"Myself,Creativity,Worry"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'ve built my wardrobe color palette around red, so I\'m happy with it, but I do get pangs when I see beautiful brunettes. I\'ve already been blue, green, black, and blonde."', '"Beautiful,Black,Green"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I think music should be scary. Music is an exorcism.', '"Music,Think,Scary"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"\'Dog Days\' was recorded with pens and the wall, and half a stolen drum kit that was out of tune, in what was basically a cupboard. The only instrument I could really play was my voice, so we just layered everything a hundred times. It was enthusiasm over skill."', '"Skill,Voice,Dog"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I love performing outside because it\'s as if the heavens are open and the elements become part of the stage show as well - you know, the wind and the rain and the thunder. It\'s almost as if there\'s a sense of invocation in performance."', '"Love,Rain,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m a choir girl gone horribly, desperately wrong."', '"Wrong,Girl,Gone"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I look really odd in jeans and a hoodie - it doesn\'t feel or seem right.', '"Look,Feel,Jeans"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m a light sleeper. I\'ve never been one of those people who can put their head down and suddenly everything disappears. Nighttime is the time I get most scared, anxious or worried. In those darker moments before waking or sleeping is when I feel most, I don\'t know, I can turn on myself, and my imagination can take me dark places."', '"Time,Imagination,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I quite like the drama of an encore. I think an encore is for those artists who are inclined to do dramatic gestures, and I certainly would say I am inclined towards them."', '"I Am,Drama,Dramatic"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I think an encore is perfectly acceptable, but I find it so weird when people do two or three."', '"Weird,People,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Look, if Givenchy is going to lend you a dress, I\'m not going to turn it down. I would wear that dress to just go out and buy a pint of milk if they would lend it to me."', '"Look,Me,Dress"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I have this sensation of being in flight all the time, but being on stage is like creating a sanctuary in which you can completely lose yourself. The bits of your personality that you keep under wraps in ordinary life, you can let them run free."', '"Life,Time,Personality"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m just a black hole for stuff. No one should ever hand me anything, because I get so easily distracted. I\'ll be like, \'Oh, look, something shiny!\' I\'m glad I never learned how to drive. I would be really dangerous."', '"Black,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve got some incredible fans actually - so loyal and they make me birthday cards and Christmas cards. I got this package of poems and artwork based around the songs. They\'ve got this thing called \'Floetry\' where they all have to put in artwork. They\'ve set up their own competitions and stuff which is kind of amazing.', '"Birthday,Amazing,Christmas"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve got quite a vivid imagination and I\'m easily overwhelmed by sensations and things that are beautiful or scary. I don\'t think I\'ve ever seen a ghost - I think I\'m probably haunted by my own ghosts than real ones.', '"Imagination,Beautiful,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Growing up, I always wanted to be in punk bands, so I\'m really enjoying the harder, heavier element. It\'s always been my dream to have people moshing at my gig, kind of that really feral element of the music coming out more. I love crowd-surfing."', '"Love,Music,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"My room is like an antique shop, full of junk, and weird stuff. There\'s a big sword in there. And a taxidermy bird, and a couple of birdcages. And a lot of newspaper cuttings. I used to have a weird thing about cutting out morbid headlines from newspapers, and collecting them. I was fascinated with drowning, which is kind of strange."', '"Bird,Weird,Sword"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"But I was always much more interested in reading fashion magazines than I was music magazines when I was a teenager. Just that sense of romanticism and escapism and the dream of it has always been quite alluring to me, as well as that sense of becoming a character through clothes."', '"Music,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I was having a conversation with my father and he was talking about this thing - strangeness and charm. It\'s actually the name of the two smallest particles that there are when you split the atom, so I wrote a song around it. I even managed to fit the word \'hydrogen\' in there. Isn\'t that a nice thing for scientists to call them though?"', '"Father,Song,Conversation"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"It would be too frightening for me to consider myself a role model. But I like the idea of not being afraid of letting your imagination rule you, to feel the freedom of expression, to let creativity be your overwhelming drive rather than other things."', '"Freedom,Imagination,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'ve got my ideal job. I like to sing, I like to dance, I like to bang drums and dress up, and someone pays me - it\'s incredible."', '"Me,Dress,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I dyed my hair red when I was ten and when I was 11 - in my goth period - I dyed it black and I was really into witchcraft. I made mini shrines in my bedroom with candles and tried to cast spells to make the boy in the next class fall in love with me. I don\'t think he did.', '"Love,Black,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"There\'s such an extreme feeling to be in love, especially in quite an emotionally destructive relationship, where you\'re both kind of really bad for each other, but you love each other so much. Those extreme emotions, I think, can only be described with extreme imagery."', '"Love,Relationship,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'You should have high expectations for yourself and others should come second.', '"Yourself,Expectations,Others"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"The stage is a place where I can be wholly myself. Even though you\'re in front of people almost to be judged, it is a place without judgement."', '"Myself,People,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"The release of \'Lungs\' was so hard. It was terrifying, because it was the first time doing everything. The first experiences of media exposure were almost paralysing. I spent a lot of time crying on the floor of the studio - it sent me a bit mad."', '"Time,Me,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When I first started, especially because I got the Critics\' Choice before I\'d released an album, there was a lot of scrutiny on what my character was, what my background was, what colour my hair was. I fought quite hard for the music to overtake the personality aspect."', '"Music,Personality,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve always been attracted to romantic secondhand clothes. But my style developed as I started going to these strange raves where everybody had these very definitive costumes.', '"Romantic,Style,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I used to dress like an eight-year-old boy. Traveling has inspired me to be more experimental.', '"Me,Dress,Boy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"\'Spectrum\' is in part a disco song. But we play it hard, and it\'s a real euphoric, wailing tune. It\'s kind of like a total house anthem, in a way, but it seems to be going down really well. We\'ve got all the grunge kids going mad for disco house raves."', '"Song,Way,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"My siblings and I were friends with the boys who would become our stepbrothers - we grew up on the same street. I feel very special to have these amazing people in my life and if we hadn\'t all moved into this big house together I think I would have missed out on that, because we would have drifted apart."', '"Life,Amazing,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I am obsessed with the whole Victoriana thing, the whole Jack the Ripper London era, the grayness of it, the haunted feeling of it, all ancient and bloody."', '"I Am,Feeling,Bloody"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m down to bleach my eyebrows again. I tell you what, though - that didn\'t go down well with my boyfriend. Girls love it. Guys, not so into it."', '"Love,Down,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I can\'t wait to get on stage, because there you don\'t worry about whether you\'ll ever get married because your life is insane, or whether you\'ll ever have another boyfriend again, you don\'t worry about the typical boundaries of how your life has to be."', '"Life,Wait,Worry"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When making the first album, I think I wrote a song about every six months. The first album was so much about the vocals carrying it."', '"Song,First,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'Music can tear me up inside.', '"Music,Me,Inside"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"What I really like seeing from the stage is people having their own moments, when people are doing some performance of their own."', '"People,Doing,Performance"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m pretty obsessed with Stevie Nicks from her style to her voice. I like watching her on YouTube and her old performances, the way she moves and everything."', '"Style,YouTube,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"During the songs, you transcend yourself. The best way to be in the performance is to be without pause and be essentially in the moment, in that moment of expression."', '"Best,Moment,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'d gone from being this art student messing about with music to this girl with a record deal, magazine front covers and all this hype. In many ways, it was everything I ever wanted, but when it happened all I felt was total, paralysing fear."', '"Art,Music,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"If you asked me to go back to being 14 or 15, I couldn\'t - it was a terrifying time. I was so awkward in my own skin. I used to hide behind my hair because I was so ridiculously self-conscious."', '"Time,Me,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I can\'t ever seem to shake the feeling that when things are really good it essentially means that things are going to go really bad. When I feel calm and settled, there is always an underlying feeling of impending doom... I don\'t think that it\'s healthy."', '"Good,Calm,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'m completely in love with the world but also terrified of it. It creates some overwhelming feelings. Wanting to battle out that joy and fear is part of my music.', '"Love,Music,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Touring, and being in a band, it\'s almost like the other stuff, the other parts of life, get put on hold."', '"Life,Band,Hold"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I definitely have a real self-destructive streak.', '"Real,Streak,Self-Destructive"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I feel a responsibility to the fans who have paid to see me and I want to give as good a show as I possibly can.', '"Good,Me,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'ve always been able to just concoct a melody quite easily - it\'s just kind of instinct, really. You\'ve got to channel your subconscious."', '"Always,Your,Able"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Going to parties usually makes me feel depressed, just because I have such social fear after meeting people."', '"Fear,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"The Teenage Cancer Trust does incredible work supporting and caring for teenagers and young adults with cancer, and it\'s a cause that is really close to me and my family."', '"Work,Family,Trust"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m quite glad I never learned to play the guitar, because I think I\'d write songs that were more classically structured. As it is, I\'ve had to create my own way of writing, which isn\'t typical. Everything\'s a big crescendo."', '"Guitar,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'Music to me is so internal. It\'s physical and it\'s emotional. Whereas fashion is so much about the external that it\'s almost like a break. It\'s not inner turmoil. It\'s total escapism.', '"Music,Me,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Music is my way out. I keep things locked up and never say anything. I guess in order to say something to one person, I have to sing it to a couple of thousand. It doesn\'t make for healthy relationships."', '"Music,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m one of those people that is up for most things. When I was offered to sing at the Oscars I was like, \'Yeah, I want to know what that\'s like!\' I\'m always curious to know what things are like - as long as you\'re not compromising who you are."', '"Long,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"The first album, for better or for worse, was done over from the ages of 17-22, with a couple of different producers. Some of it was recorded in an old swimming pool, some of it was recorded in a synagogue - it kind of was all over the place."', '"Swimming,Better,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I think I should get a bigger between-the-song persona, so then I\'m not wandering around the stage like some mad old auntie that\'s saying hello to people and falling over."', '"People,Falling,Mad"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I like to wear clothes that I will wear when I am an old lady.', '"I Am,Lady,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I made music with my friend, who we called Isabella Machine to which I was Florence Robot. When I was about an hour away from my first gig, I still didn\'t have a name, so I thought \'Okay, I\'ll be Florence Robot/Isa Machine\', before realising that name was so long it\'d drive me mad."', '"Music,Me,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'d experimented with so many different types of music. I had these folky songs I\'d written and recorded, but something wasn\'t quite right."', '"Music,Right,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I didn\'t want to become a personality, I wanted to be a musician, but because I didn\'t have an album to stand by yet it was hard for people to see that. But now, two albums in, I\'m happy with things."', '"Personality,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"The aesthetic came along the way, I think - just through experimenting, and going on tour, and trying stuff out on stage, having fun with it, and not taking it too seriously. If I had a ballgown at home, I\'d wear it onstage. If I found something in a charity shop, I\'d wear it. That\'s where it grew from - just wanting to play dress-up."', '"Home,Fun,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'m really careful with what the music gets put with, and we say no to so much stuff, loads of it, for things that might quadruple the sales of my album. But if it doesn\'t fit then it doesn\'t fit, you know?"', '"Music,Know,Careful"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"Bono told me how to dance in high heels and he also told me about U2\'s Glastonbury performance and how everything that could have possibly gone wrong went wrong, including him ripping his trousers on stage. I think he was lunging and his trousers ripped! He was telling me how he had to find a new way of performing that didn\'t involve moving."', '"Me,Way,New"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"At the beginning of my career I was going through a really weird phase of dressing in boys clothes. I would only wear one American Apparel T-shirt and shorts and brogues the whole year round. Not the same T-shirt, obviously, but one style of American Apparel T-shirt. I think I was going through a tomboy stage."', '"T-Shirt,Style,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I think I just get excited by music, and, like, singing is a very physical thing. It releases endorphins in your body. You\'re using almost muscle in there, and I think that adrenaline really helps to kind of make the songs fresh every time."', '"Time,Music,Singing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I saw \'The Artist.\' It\'s really beautiful and it\'s all done to the letter with all the silent film techniques. The costumes were amazing and the dog is so good.', '"Good,Amazing,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I love that sense of release as you throw yourself into the crowd as hundreds of arms are carrying you.', '"Love,Yourself,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'My style of playing is more enthusiasm and instinct than skill.', '"Skill,Style,Enthusiasm"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I feel things in quite an intense way. I\'m not actually the most intense person.', '"Way,Feel,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I try to write lyrics so that they won\'t age, which sort of leaves you with the big subjects like death and love and sex and violence."', '"Love,Death,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I love Lady Gaga and I love Katy Perry and R&B and rap music... I love big, American pop music."', '"Love,Music,Lady"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve always been a bit of a decorator. I think if I wasn\'t a singer I\'d probably be in stage setting or interior design or something. I like clutter and I\'m quite visually greedy. I can\'t have things to be plain; I have to have things looking interesting... maybe I\'m just a frustrated interior designer stuck in a singing career.', '"Design,Singing,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'The sense of jubilee for music and what we\'re making is always genuine.', '"Music,Genuine,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"You know, people always ask, \'What are you like offstage?\' And I always say, \'Well, I\'m completely normal and mellow.\'"', '"People,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve just never been a tracksuit-wearer.', '"Never,Just,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"On stage, you can use your emotions. It\'s the place where you can channel them. They have a purpose."', '"Purpose,Emotions,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I get in fights with my sister all the time. She comes on the road with me and we fight - like sisters do.', '"Time,Fight,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'It\'s very flattering when you look into the crowd and people have made an effort and dressed in your style.', '"Look,Effort,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When something really hits me, it makes me want to either jump off something really high or lie down and be buried. I want people to get hit and caught by my music."', '"Music,Me,Lie"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'Maybe in music you\'re making an auditory environment and maybe you change your environment around you to suit your own way.', '"Change,Music,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I always seem to feel that everything is about to cave in on me. I think that maybe music is my protection from that and in some senses it\'s an outlet to turn it into something euphoric: embracing the eventual decline.', '"Music,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I started off singing in church as a child. The sound of voices coming together, that was my first moment of touching something outside of myself."', '"Myself,Moment,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'When I\'m singing I\'m always trying to get to the highest point possible. I\'d fly to the top of Buckingham Palace to sing to the queen.', '"Fly,Queen,Singing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I\'ve been having this really weird anxiety dream about arriving too late or too early, and the people in charge are like, \'You have to leave! You have to go back to the hotel and get ready!\' And I use the wrong exit, and I\'m running down the red carpet in pyjamas, like, \'No! Don\'t look at me!\'"', '"Look,Me,Hotel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I got to live out my 11-year-old fantasies - I got to go on stage with Green Day. Billie Joe called my name from the stage. \'Dookie\' was the first album I ever bought. I covered the whole of \'Nimrod\' and he\'d heard it. That was like the 11-year-old girl dreamed.', '"Green,Day,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'I\'ve learned not to hide behind a veil of irony - to talk about my work in a more honest way.', '"Work,Way,Hide"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When I am with my family, then I can just sort of switch off. It\'s kind of weird, because I go back and I go into this bedroom that I have had since I was a teenager. It is like this parallel universe, because one minute I am on the red carpet and then the next I am hiding out in this room I have had since I was 15."', '"Family,I Am,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"When you play, it\'s like you know that there are people out there who are hearing it for the first time, and I think that\'s really important."', '"Time,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', 'My mum wanted me to go to university.', '"Me,Go,University"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd75', '"I always wanted to sound like a man, like Jeff Buckley or Tom Waits."', '"Man,Always,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"\'The Moon Rabbit\' is laying against the bunker, dreaming and thinking about life and dreaming the impossible possible and creating its own true stories."', '"Life,Moon,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', 'I make work not to give answers but to question things.', '"Work,Things,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I used to get a lot of rubber ducks on my birthdays as presents because, you know, I make rubber ducks. But then I get the ugliest ones with a neck, ugly colors, and devil ears. I don\'t like those."', '"Devil,Colors,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I make work a bit like how you mix cocktails - with ingredients like budget, history and location."', '"Work,History,Budget"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I make big objects that are simple, bright and clear, kind of ironic but hopefully funny because I love the shapes, and I get inspiration from toys and books, and I believe in art for everyone."', '"Funny,Love,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"If you work in a public space, you have to be aware that no one is buying a ticket."', '"Work,Space,Buying"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I want people to get inspired by public space - their space. People tend to forget about it because they do the daily thing, but putting up these sculptures breaks the routine."', '"Space,Daily,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', 'I\'ve always said the rubber duck is a yellow catalyst.', '"Duck,Always,Yellow"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"My sculptures cause an uproar, astonishment, and put a smile on your face."', '"Smile,Face,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"The Internet is fascinating but also stupid in a way. You only see two-dimensional images, and you think you\'ve seen it and know it."', '"Stupid,Internet,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I love it when people travel to see one of my works, and I always make time to meet and talk with them."', '"Love,Time,Travel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', 'That is the effect of my sculptures in the public domain: people are making contact with each other again.', '"People,Public Domain,Contact"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I wanted to use the hippo to get people out of their homes, away from the Internet and the TV, and to explore London with a new perspective."', '"Internet,Perspective,New"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"The slugs are ascending this steep city staircase that leads up to a huge Catholic church, essentially signifying their slow crawl towards death. The work reminds us of religion, mortality, natural decay, and the slow suffocation of commercialized societies."', '"Work,Death,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"I really hate rubber ducks, actually."', '"Hate,Ducks,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', 'I think places that need the rubber duck the most are the ones in distress.', '"Duck,Need,Places"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd76', '"In Holland, we have a saying: \'A knife cuts on two sides.\' With the rubber duck, I\'m trying to show people what they haven\'t been seeing in their public space. When the rubber duck is there and when it\'s gone, you know."', '"Space,Duck,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Curtain! Fast music! Light! Ready for the last finale! Great! The show looks good, the show looks good!"', '"Good,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Let us hope that for many it does mean the end of trouble so far as earning a livelihood is concerned, that it means happy and comfortable home living honestly earned. But there are other troubles ahead for her, and plenty of hard work."', '"Work,Hope,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"But it is only through constant, faithful endeavor by the girl herself that the goal eventually is reached."', '"Girl,Faithful,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Beauty, of course, is the most important requirement and the paramount asset of the applicant."', '"Beauty,Important,Asset"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"To illustrate what I mean, an apt dancer may be in thorough unison with the others in that particular group, and at the same time reveal a difference in dancing temperament, rhythm or technique; she may phrase, accentuate or actually interpret differently."', '"Time,Group,Difference"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"And, I may add, from what totally unexpected sources come many of those who from the comparatively modest beginning in the chorus rise to the heights of really great achievement in the theatrical profession."', '"Great,Achievement,Unexpected"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Half of the great comedians I\'ve had in my shows and that I paid a lot of money to and who made my customers shriek were not only not funny to me, but I couldn\'t understand why they were funny to anybody."', '"Funny,Money,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', 'How little the public realizes what a girl must go through before she finally appears before the spotlight that is thrown upon the stage.', '"Stage,Go,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', 'I don\'t have a very quick sense of humor.', '"Humor,Sense Of Humor,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"It is the task of several months and it is a fact that a girl, either while rehearsing or actually playing, may be training for some character or feature in some future production not yet definitely fixed even in my own mind."', '"Future,Character,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Not only may she unconsciously register a favorable impression with my associates and me, but she may also suggest something by her work that will lead to some new and novel feature in a forthcoming production."', '"Work,Me,New"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', 'They all hope I will go broke and I wouldn\'t like to cause them displeasure.', '"Hope,Will,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd77', '"Yes, there is plenty of hard work for them in addition to that which they do when they appear, smiling and happy, when the curtain goes up. Giving a performance is the least of their worries."', '"Work,Hard Work,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'There is no beginning and no end in music. Some people want it to end. But it goes on.', '"Music,Beginning,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"I found that the flute was too limiting. Soon I bought a microphone, then loudspeakers, then an echo, then a synthesiser. Much later I threw the flute away; it was a sort of process."', '"Process,Microphone,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"We don\'t make a distinction between an acoustic instrument as a source of sound and any sound in the air outside or on a manufactured tape. It\'s all electric energy, anyway."', '"Energy,Air,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'Kraftwerk has become historic and is now exposed in museums.', '"Now,Become,Museums"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'Our studio is in the middle of an oil refinery. There\'s smoke and fire around it and when you emerge from the studio you hear this hissing sound all around you.', '"Fire,Smoke,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"Kraftwerk isn\'t a band. It\'s a concept. We call it \'Die Menschmaschine,\' which means \'the human machine.\'"', '"Die,Band,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'A person doing experimental music must be responsible for the results of the experiments. They could be very dangerous emotionally.', '"Music,Person,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'We are not the band. I am me. Ralf is Ralf. And Kraftwerk is a vehicle for our ideas.', '"Me,I Am,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'We\'re just private people.', '"People,Just,Private"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"As for ourselves, we love our machines."', '"Love,Machines,Ourselves"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"Our method of speaking is interrupted, hard-edged... a lot of consonants and noises."', '"Our,Lot,Method"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"We are more like vehicles, a part of our mensch machine, our man-machine. Sometimes we play the music, sometimes the music plays us, sometimes... it plays."', '"Music,Sometimes,More"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', 'Emotion\' is a strange word.', '"Strange,Emotion,Word"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"The image of the robot is very important to us, it\'s very stimulating to people\'s imaginations."', '"People,Important,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"We always found that many people are robots without knowing it. The interpreters of classical music, Horowitz for example, they are like robots, making a reproduction of the music which is always the same. It\'s automatic, and they do it as if it were natural, which is not true."', '"Music,True,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd78', '"In Paris, the people go in the Metro, they move, they go to their offices, 8 a.m. in the morning - it\'s like remote control."', '"Morning,Control,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd79', 'Any kind of peanut butter/chocolate concoction is my jam.', '"Peanut,Jam,Kind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd79', '"I may have the \'Twilight: Breaking Dawn\' soundtrack, which I\'ve been told is embarrassing, but come on, there are some good songs on there."', '"Good,Dawn,Twilight"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', '"Life does not accommodate you, it shatters you. It is meant to, and it couldn\'t do it better. Every seed destroys its container or else there would be no fruition."', '"Life,Better,Seed"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', 'No matter how old a mother is she watches her middle-aged children for signs of improvement.', '"Improvement,Children,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', '"The crucial task of old age is balance: keeping just well enough, just brave enough, just gay and interested and starkly honest enough to remain a sentient human being."', '"Age,Old Age,Brave"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', '"Age puzzles me. I thought it was a quiet time. My seventies were interesting and fairly serene, but my eighties are passionate. I grow more intense as I age."', '"Time,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', '"It is not easy to be sure that being yourself is worth the trouble, but we do know it is our sacred duty."', '"Yourself,Duty,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7a', 'My kitchen linoleum is so black and shiny that I waltz while I wait for the kettle to boil. This pleasure is for the old who live alone.', '"Alone,Black,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', '"I think we should look forward to death more than we do. Of course everybody hates to go to bed or miss anything, but dying is really the only chance we\'ll get to rest."', '"Death,Chance,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', '"If men could get pregnant, abortion would be a sacrament."', '"Men,Abortion,Sacrament"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', 'I approve of anyone wearing what the establishment says you must not wear.', '"Wear,Must,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', 'Everybody\'s scared for their ass. There aren\'t too many people ready to die for racism. They\'ll kill for racism but they won\'t die for racism.', '"Die,People,Ready"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', 'When a system of oppression has become institutionalized it is unnecessary for individuals to be oppressive.', '"Oppression,System,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7b', 'The question arises whether all lawyers are the same. This is like asking whether everything that gets into a sewer is garbage.', '"Everything,Garbage,Lawyers"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"CBS fought very hard on this because it believed and believes that there\'s a principle at stake here. The principle is that Dan Rather doesn\'t work for the police, and that people that speak to Dan Rather understand that he\'s a journalist and not a police agent."', '"Work,Police,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"It just seems to be a human trait to want to protect the speech of people with whom we agree. For the First Amendment, that is not good enough. So it is really important that we protect First Amendment rights of people no matter what side of the line they are on."', '"Good,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I just had the sense that at least the books that I had read about law just didn\'t really have enough of that.', '"Law,Enough,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"No other country in the world gives protection like that, but it is not absolute protection. People sometimes meet that high burden and win libel suits, and in those cases I think they ought to win."', '"World,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"It has something to do with the facts and the law and who the judges are. So I think lawyers sometimes exaggerate their role in winning and losing. Lawyers do have a role, and a major role, but they\'re not the only players in this game."', '"Game,Winning,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'Here we have a situation where a defendant in a case agrees to an interview with Dan Rather. It happened to be not confidential. But it was an interview with Dan Rather.', '"Situation,Interview,Happened"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I try to do that in this book without preaching - to try to do as you just said that you really have to defend the First Amendment rights of everybody.', '"Try,First,Rights"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I would say that the Pentagon Papers case of 1971 - in which the government tried to block the The New York Times and The Washington Post that they obtained from a secret study of how we got involved in the war in Vietnam - that is probably the most important case.', '"War,Government,New"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'My role in it was not as central as it was in some of the later cases considering I was younger then and I was playing a role of co-counsel on the case.', '"Younger,Role,Playing"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"The government would be able to go to court with respect to newspaper articles, broadcast pieces and the like that they thought were bad or harmful or even against the government and try to block them."', '"Respect,Government,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"When I began we did not really have a lot of First Amendment law. It is really surprising to think of it this way, but a lot of the law - most of the law that relates to the First Amendment freedom of the press in America - is really within living memory."', '"Freedom,Law,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"It is within the last quarter century or thirty years. And a lot of that law has turned out to be very, very protective of the press and the public\'s right to know."', '"Law,Know,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"I think we have some serious problems now, but, if you look back over the last thirty or forty years that my book deals with, I think we are in better shape now than we would have been if all of those cases had not come down."', '"Look,Problems,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I really did try to write it so that an educated public that cares about issues like this doesn\'t have to be a lawyer and can read it and understand it.', '"Lawyer,Understand,Educated"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'It\'s not like learning how to hit a curve ball in baseball.', '"Learning,Ball,Baseball"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I really try at least to come back and answer the question as to whether that was really the best way to do that and was I really thinking straight and how did my opponents behave and how did the judges behave was needed.', '"Best,Thinking,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I am really impressed by lawyers who write books and tell us that they never lost a case. Most lawyers who have never lost a case have not had enough hard cases. But there are very difficult cases out there.', '"I Am,Lost,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"I still owe a duty of loyalty to my clients and former clients, so I cannot specify which clients I did not especially find congenial, but the cause was the same."', '"Loyalty,Duty,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I think that it is important for people to understand that whether a good-guy or a bad-guy wins a case is less important than what the law is that the case results in.', '"Law,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"So sometimes the facts are good and sometimes the facts are bad, the important thing from the point of view of a principle as broad and important as freedom of speech is that the courts articulate and set forth in a very protective way what those principles are."', '"Freedom,Good,View"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'There are some circumstances in which the First Amendment interest comes up against another interest that is really important and in which we have to make a decision in a particular case as to which is more important.', '"Decision,Important,Circumstances"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'CBS exhausted the Texas courts. They went from the trial court to the intermediate court to the highest court.', '"Court,Exhausted,Courts"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', 'I know a lot of reporters certainly will go to jail to defend confidential sources. Some have even gone to jail for an issue like this. But I can\'t say that\'s the norm.', '"Will,Know,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"I mean the idea of this is that it\'s a good thing for the public to hear interviews like this and that there will be an inevitable amount of fewer interviews if people that the press talks to wind up thinking, well, it\'s not really a CBS correspondent."', '"Good,Thinking,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"I think that the very fact that CBS fought and fought and fought in Texas, in New York."', '"New,Think,Texas"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"If the word gets out, if the perception exists that by speaking to a CBS journalist you are, therefore, inevitably, immediately speaking to the police, I don\'t think there\'s any doubt but that people won\'t talk. And, therefore, the public won\'t learn."', '"Police,People,Perception"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"It is not to benefit CBS, not to benefit its reporters. On this one, the entire basis of it is this is a way to get more information, more important information to the public. And that\'s why so many states recognize this."', '"Information,Way,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"The principle though remains the same, and the important thing is CBS fought hard, very hard, to protect that principle and will fight again."', '"Fight,Important,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"The question at the end of the day was, the courts having found there was no defense, a producer about to go to jail, should CBS in effect tell the producer go to jail even though there is no law at all that we can use to get you out of jail?"', '"End Of The Day,Day,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"This is going right to the police. So, it\'s a very dangerous precedent."', '"Police,Dangerous,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7c', '"Were this not Texas, were there not a state where there were no protections at all and where the law was clear on that, I think CBS and Mary Mapes and Dan Rather and all of us had a very good chance of winning. So this is an ongoing battle about an issue of principle."', '"Good,Chance,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7e', 'I\'ve been knocked down more than any heavyweight champion in history.', '"History,Champion,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7e', '"Fear was absolutely necessary. Without it, I would have been scared to death."', '"Death,Fear,Scared"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7e', 'The fighter loses more than his pride in the fight; he loses part of his future. He\'s a step closer to the slum he came from.', '"Future,Fight,Pride"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7e', 'For if you train hard and responsibly your confidence surges to a maximum.', '"Confidence,Hard,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"My cerebral cortex, the gray matter that MIT neuroscientist Steven Pinker likens to \'a large sheet of two-dimensional tissue that has been wadded up to fit inside the spherical skull,\' is riddled instead of whole."', '"Matter,Gray,Inside"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Dementia is, after all, a symptom of organic brain damage. It is a condition, a disorder of the central nervous system, brought about in my case by a viral assault on brain tissue. When the assault wiped out certain intellectual processes, it also affected emotional processes."', '"Brain,Nervous,Organic"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"At 93, so deep in dementia that she didn\'t remember any details of her life, my mother somehow still knew songs."', '"Life,Remember,Details"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'One of the strangest aspects of living with certain kinds of memory loss is knowing that the forgetting is happening.', '"Memory,Living,Loss"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"I used to be able to think. My brain\'s circuits were all connected, and I had spark, a quickness of mind that let me function well in the world."', '"Brain,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'I became demented overnight. Sudden onset is one factor that distinguishes my form of dementia from the more common form associated with Alzheimer\'s disease.', '"More,Disease,Dementia"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"For those who turn to literary biography for salacious details, \'Flannery\' will disappoint. It is the biography of someone who had very little chance to live in the conventional sense, to experience events."', '"Experience,Chance,Details"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Though my poems are about evenly split between traditionally formal work that uses rhyme and meter and classical structure, and work that is freer, I feel that the music of language remains at the core of it all. Sound, rhythm, repetition, compression - these elements of my poetry are also elements of my prose."', '"Work,Music,Poetry"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"I think one of the primary themes in my work is the paradox of memory, at once fundamental to our sense of who we are and yet elusive, ever-changing, fragmentary. One way to look at this is to say that, therefore, we ourselves are elusive, ever-changing and fragmentary to ourselves."', '"Work,Look,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'Fiction about mining has a long tradition - Emile Zola\'s \'Germinal\' and Upton Sinclair\'s \'King Coal\' come to mind - and most readers will be aware of the industry\'s harsh conditions.', '"King,Mind,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"In \'A Poetics of Optics,\' Equi writes that \'all images bank on alchemy.\' This idea captures her fundamental sense of poetry as turning common material into something rare and valuable."', '"Poetry,Bank,Rare"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"\'The Art Student\'s War\' is, at its core, a traditional American wartime love story. As such, it is timely and engrossing. By the end, all its principal characters \'have been to Hell and back.\'"', '"Love,War,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'Neurologists have a host of clinical tests that let them observe what a brain-damaged patient can and cannot do.', '"Patient,Cannot,Observe"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"My wife is a painter, musician, and fiber artist. We married in 1993, and as she worked, I found that my reading about art was helping me understand what she was doing, just as seeing her work gave me a language with which to speak of art."', '"Work,Art,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"A new laboratory technique, positron emission tomography, uses radioactively labeled oxygen or glucose that essentially lights up specific and different areas of the brain being activated when a person speaks words or sees words or hears words, revealing the organic location for areas of behavioral malfunction."', '"Brain,Words,New"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Dementia resembles delirium in the same way an ultra-marathon resembles a dash across the street. Same basic components, vastly different scale. If you\'ve run delirium\'s course once or twice in your life, try to imagine a version that never ends."', '"Life,Street,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"In the spring of 1993, I married Beverly and moved to the woods. This is something I could never have imagined myself doing."', '"Myself,Woods,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Through his long, productive career, Paul Theroux has mixed nonfiction books about exotic travel with novels set in exotic places. Africa, Singapore, Hong Kong, Honduras - he lives in and writes about places most of us never see."', '"Travel,Long,See"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Music seems hard-wired into our very being. It moves us, stirs us to action, sets us in motion, sticks in our memories and minds."', '"Music,Memories,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Most people imagine music playing in their heads, but some hallucinate music; some cannot sleep because of the soundtrack in their mind."', '"Music,Mind,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Irish novelist John Banville has a creepy, introverted imagination."', '"Imagination,Irish,Creepy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"When memories fade, can one ever really return home?"', '"Home,Memories,Fade"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"In 1964, at the age of 39, Flannery O\'Connor died from complications of lupus. She had lived with this autoimmune disease for 14 years, primarily confined to her mother\'s farm, Andalusia, in Milledgeville, Ga."', '"Age,Mother,She"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'Flannery O\'Connor\'s brief life and slim output were nonetheless marked by piercing powers of observation.', '"Life,Observation,Slim"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"When Beverly and I got together in 1992, and I moved to be with her in the little round house she\'d built in the middle of 20 acres of woods near Amity, I found myself immersed in a natural setting that I responded to with all my being."', '"Myself,Together,Woods"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"I feel that I\'m a poet first. Not only was poetry the first genre in which I wrote, it\'s the genre that serves as the basis for my practice as a writer."', '"Poetry,Feel,Practice"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"I\'ve forgotten what it\'s like to remember. I\'ve lost the mindless confidence that a moment, an idea, a thought will be there for me later, the bravado of breezing through experience in the certainty that it will become part of my self, part of my story."', '"Experience,Moment,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"I\'m a writer who simply can\'t know what I\'m writing about until the writing lets me discover it. In a sense, my writing process embraces the gapped nature of my memory process, leaping across spaces that represent all I\'ve lost and establishing fresh patterns within all that remains."', '"Nature,Me,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"In question-and-answer sessions after a reading or during an interview, I forget the question if I\'m giving too long an answer. And at the end, I can\'t remember any of the questions. The more anxious I am about remembering, the more likely I am to forget."', '"Long,I Am,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"If I don\'t write down a thought - or an image or a line of poetry - the instant it comes to mind, it vanishes, which explains why I have pens and notebooks in my pants and coat pockets, the car, the bicycle basket, on one or two desks in every room including bathrooms and the kitchen."', '"Car,Poetry,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Elaine Equi has been publishing her observant, often playful poetry for some 30 years, extending and deepening the range of her intrinsically wry voice."', '"Poetry,Voice,Playful"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', 'A risk for a poet-novelist is imbalance: The poems can flatten into prose or lose their intensity of focus; the novels can stall amid lofty writing or literary preciousness and ignore the engine of plot and character.', '"Focus,Character,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Eliza Factor\'s first novel, \'The Mercury Fountain,\' explores what happens when a life driven by ideology confronts implacable truths of science and human nature. It also shows how leaders can inflict damage by neglecting the real needs of real people."', '"Life,Nature,Science"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd7f', '"Science trumps magical thinking: there was a reason the Incas called their mercury mine \'la mina de los muertos,\' the mine of the dead. Building a life and a community upon principles that ignore such realities is doomed to fail."', '"Life,Science,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"Sometimes you have to exercise your insanity, to really make it strong."', '"Exercise,Sometimes,Insanity"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"The hardest portion of English, I must say it: Idioms."', '"Hardest,Say,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"I really like the Doors. I like Kevin Spacey, Bruce Springsteen, Will Farrell, Reggie Watts, Tina Turner, who is also very hot, Tracy Chapman. Beethoven."', '"Hot,Will,Doors"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"When I see things that are inspiring, I must write a song about it. Some people make a t-shirt or slap something on a wall with paint, but I must make music and freestyle rap."', '"Music,T-Shirt,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"I wrote a techno song after I was deported. I was in America for a little bit, but then I was deported back to Germany. I was very sad."', '"Sad,Song,America"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'More exposure has give to me more discipline because I am seeing that more people are wanting to observe what I am making/filming/singing; this does motivate me to make videos for every week.', '"Discipline,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"I am a musician who also does love to explore the world in many ways, so my approaching with my songs, videos, and haikus is: \'Make It Real.\'"', '"Love,World,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'I love to work with performers that are very different to me.', '"Love,Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'Dirk Nowitzki has been my hero for many years.', '"Hero,Been,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'I am a crazy Maverick fan. I would go there if Dallas was a great entertainment center.', '"Great,I Am,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'I think many people are finding things I do very funny and strange.', '"Funny,People,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'I do not really know what is my interview and performance style.', '"Style,Know,Performance"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"I wrote a techno song about the four things I love in Germany to make myself happy, which are my grandfather, my two poodle pets, bread, and a strange but delicious Turkish dish called Doener Kebab."', '"Love,Myself,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', 'I like to make my name of songs strange.', '"Name,Strange,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd80', '"Dirk is like the German Moses, invincible and inspiring. That is why \'His Name Is Dirk\' must be the Official Fan Song for Dirk Nowitzki."', '"Song,Name,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Imperfection is perfection.', '"Perfection,Imperfection"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I think Sydney has so much natural beauty; it\'s just a beautiful city.', '"Beauty,Beautiful,Natural Beauty"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I think, in the early years, my biggest influences would have been... Daft Punk was a huge one for me, I bought their main record when I was nine; at a young age, I was into music. The Prodigy, Gorillaz were big ones."', '"Age,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I did a few DJ gigs at empty clubs, sort of as a warm-up set before Flume was a thing. I did one when I got big enough, and I had five friends come down, and they were the only ones dancing. That was one of my earliest ones. I was super nervous."', '"DJ,Enough,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"For me, I actually come from an electronic dance music background: house music, electro house, trance music, even. When I was coming out of school, basically, I discovered Brain Fever, Flying Lotus, J Dilla and all that. That was when I got excited about hip-hop and when the Flume project started."', '"Music,Brain,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"There\'s a lot of creativity in the industry, but I don\'t necessarily think that the most creative DJs or producers are always the biggest ones."', '"Creativity,Always,DJs"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I struggled with the pressure of having the successful record after the first record. Second album syndrome. I\'m living proof; it\'s very real. It was like a psychological battle to be creative. I used to never feel pressure to be creative; it\'s always just been a fun thing. And then suddenly it\'s my job, and people are asking, \'Where\'s the record?\'"', '"Battle,Fun,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"My main inspirations come from early \'90s Trance, the French electro movement round \'06, then a bunch of artists like Flying Lotus, J Dilla, Moby, The Prodigy. So I\'d say it\'s some kind of experimental electronica with a strong hip hop influence. It\'s chilled, but people can still get super crazy and dance to it."', '"Crazy,Influence,People"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I think the thing that L.A. had on Sydney is an awesome music scene, especially for what I do."', '"Music,Awesome,Sydney"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I was an avid Pokemon card collector.', '"Collector,Card,Avid"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Everyone can write their melodies and chords and pianos and guitars, but what hasn\'t been discovered yet are tones and textures, and that\'s very exciting. Probably the No. 1 most important thing in my music is not to sound like anyone else."', '"Music,Important,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"In the dressing room, we\'ve just made it really Zen: low lighting, lots of candles, and fresh, healthy food."', '"Food,Room,Fresh"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"There\'s a lot of creativity in the industry, but I don\'t necessarily think that the most creative DJs or producers are always the biggest ones. I think it would be nice to see more of an open culture to different music. I think that\'s happening. With Spotify, I think people are discovering a lot of artists they might not discover otherwise."', '"Music,Culture,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'ve never been a rap guy, I don\'t really know that much about rap music, to be honest. I like it, but I think what really happened was just my music seems to work so well with rap music."', '"Work,Music,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I know how to make a record that commercial radio or Triple J will smash now... It\'s kind of hard to stay true and write what you would write if you didn\'t have that in your head. Because I know I can get way more airplay and get this much bigger... and that\'s what I\'m trying to avoid doing. Trying to avoid the poisons of success.', '"Success,True,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"When I heard Flying Lotus, I was like, \'Wow, okay, everything can be off the grid.\'"', '"Everything,Okay,Wow"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'m not thinking about the next record really yet. I kind of want to do a bunch of stuff with Jonathan Zawada, the guy who did the album art. I\'d like to do some crazy art installations and design some weird synthesizers and work with other people and make some fun stuff for a bit. Maybe tap into virtual reality stuff or maybe write another record."', '"Work,Art,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Back in the day, I had this fluoro pink hoodie that I thought was the coolest thing ever. Left it at a party and never saw it again. Probably the best thing that could have happened."', '"Best,Day,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Great songwriting will never die - it\'s in the DNA of music - but what\'s new and exciting is pairing that with new sounds that technology is enabling us to make.', '"Technology,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I\'d like to do some crazy art installations and design some weird synthesizers and work with other people and make some fun stuff for a bit. Maybe tap into virtual reality stuff or maybe write another record... We\'ll see.', '"Work,Art,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I don\'t think I can name any names or anything, but this is what I\'ve wanted to do for a long time: to have Flume as my creative outlet and to work on the biggest songs in the world, like pop, and come up with the idea and send it off."', '"Work,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I could do another tour, make a record that\'s very similar, do similar venues. Or I could make a different record, do different venues, and grow. It\'s exciting to take it to new places, but it\'s never been my intent to be the biggest thing in the world. That\'s not what my drive is. I want to make what I want to make, and make a living off it."', '"World,Drive,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"For me, I would prefer to not have my face on the album cover. I don\'t mind being in the public, but it\'s just not really my personality, and it\'s not really why I\'m into this. I like making art, and that\'s it. I don\'t really want to be a celebrity, seriously. I like my privacy."', '"Art,Personality,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Making sounds that literally no one has ever heard before because the software and the technology\'s never been there, and pairing that with great songwriting, then that\'s what\'s exciting for me. That\'s what I wanna do."', '"Technology,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I want to fuse the abrasive and the beautiful.', '"Beautiful,Want,Fuse"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'m just trying to work out how to write music now, because I\'ve never had the opportunity where my number-one priority is writing music. I don\'t know how my brain works yet."', '"Work,Music,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'ve grown up by the beach all my life, and I almost get anxiety if I haven\'t been swimming for a couple weeks or a month. It kind of builds up, so I try and get out as much as possible."', '"Life,Swimming,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I think at first the Flume project really started out as an online thing. I used Facebook and SoundCloud, and I think we got lucky because it felt like a bit of a golden age of those social media platforms. So I managed to create quite a solid fan base online."', '"Age,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"The thing I find frustrating about rock music is, how different can you make an acoustic drum kit sound, an electric guitar and vocals?"', '"Music,Guitar,Rock"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I\'m a really heavy sleeper. When I wake up I\'m a terrible morning person.', '"Morning,Wake Up,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'m always really curious about, you know, \'How do you deal with success psychologically?\' and all this stuff."', '"Success,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:47:00', '2023-05-29 11:47:00'),
	('393950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"There was this cereal, and it had a special promotion with a CD inside the box that had a really simple music-making program on it. I got it, and that opened my mind to being able to make music on a computer and seeing all the different layers."', '"Music,Simple,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"What it is now is basically I\'ll sit on my computer; I basically kind of play the computer as an instrument, I guess you could say. I guess I play the Mac."', '"Mac,Sit,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"For me, one of the downfalls of electronic music is that it can feel a little soulless or robotic."', '"Music,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Combining sounds that are from another universe with the classic songwriting structures never gets old for me.', '"Me,Universe,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I want to be creative in as many different environments as possible, whether it\'s doing film scores, writing for TV ads or video games - all sorts of stuff, as long as it requires writing music."', '"Music,Long,Video Games"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Along with \'Free,\' where I sing quite a bit, there are additional songs on \'Skin\' where you can hear my voice in the background - lots of \'oohs\' and \'aahs.\' But more often than not, I use my vocals to prompt other rappers and singers to feel calmer, better, bolder."', '"Free,Skin,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Every kid has a laptop; everyone can make music, so in order to stand out, I think it\'s important to find that sonic identity, I think my sonic identity - and mine is finding these weird sounds that may not necessarily sound that musical, and make them sound musical."', '"Music,Weird,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I feel like the first record was really finding my feet, figuring out what music I wanted to make... Now that I\'ve done that, I feel like I\'ve got a much clearer idea of what I want to sound like and what I want to discover. It\'s exciting."', '"Music,Feet,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'ve never been one to want to be the center of attention and be put up on stages every night. That\'s just not really my personality. I\'m comfortable with it now, but my real passion is being creative."', '"Personality,Passion,Night"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'The minute I saw the front page of the \'Daily Telegraph\' - me with my arm around the latest \'X-Factor\' contestant - I realised I\'d gone into a new realm.', '"Daily,Me,New"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'d like to actually work with a lot of other people, and whether it\'s someone who is completely unknown who I love and think is a talent, maybe I\'ll work with them, or, like, maybe I\'ll work with some of the biggest pop stars and write music for them."', '"Love,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"To me, skin is alien and kind of weird; it weirds me out. It\'s strange, but it\'s also really intimate and personal; it\'s living, organic. That\'s how I want the music to sound; I want it to feel alien and strange, but also like it\'s got a heartbeat, like it\'s got a soul, like it\'s not made by a robot."', '"Music,Me,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"What it is now is basically, I\'ll sit on my computer; I basically kind of play the computer as an instrument, I guess you could say. I guess I play the Mac. And how it works is, say - I have a program called \'Ableton Live.\' And, you know, you\'ll open it up, and it\'s just blank. There\'s nothing there. And then you start."', '"Start,Nothing,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I think I put a lot of special attention towards creating interesting textures and unique sounds. Music essentially boils down to two main elements: rhythm and melody. I feel tones and textures often get overlooked, so I like to take my time finding the right sounds."', '"Time,Music,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'It\'s quite fun to mess with the human voice. It\'s quite special in the sense that the voice is the #1 instrument that we can connect with; it doesn\'t sound too alien. I think that\'s the key is to find the line between sounding human and sounding robotic. That\'s an area that I like to explore a lot.', '"Fun,Alien,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"In the right context, you can make ugly sounds, different sounds feel right at home."', '"Home,Feel,Ugly"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'My parents used to play me this album when I couldn\'t go to sleep. It was called \'Deep Forest.\' I think it was a self-titled record. It\'s actually still one of my favorite albums of all time.', '"Time,Me,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '\'Sleepless\' was the first thing that came out and really gained a lot of traction online.', '"First,Online,Out"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"The thing I find frustrating about rock music is, how different can you make an acoustic drum kit sound, an electric guitar and vocals? It\'s very stuck, whereas with electronic music, new sounds are being created."', '"Music,Guitar,New"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"This life and this job and this position that I\'m put in, it forces you to grow up quick. I definitely got dropped in the deep end."', '"Life,Grow,End"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I always regret leaving home if I don\'t get at least four or five surfs in the week before I leave. I try to be in the water as much as possible before leaving, and it\'s the one thing I miss massively."', '"Home,Water,Regret"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Australia is so influenced by America. It\'s kind of in-between the U.K. and the States.', '"America,Australia,In-Between"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'The music I was making for people not to dance to was the one they were dancing to.', '"Music,People,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I\'m a huge fan of Flying Lotus. I like The XX\'s stuff.', '"Flying,Fan,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'ve been having meetings with people, just everywhere in the world, and it\'s like, \'Hey, really love you to work with me, send me some ideas.\' That\'s the crazy part."', '"Love,Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"It\'s always the first 10,000 SoundCloud listens; that was definitely a big moment, seeing the online stuff grow and crowds grow."', '"Moment,Grow,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"With Spotify, I think people are discovering a lot of artists they might not discover otherwise."', '"People,Spotify,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I was delivering papers when I was, like, 10 or 11, and I\'d always daydream about being an artist as a full-time thing."', '"Always,Artist,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I feel like I need to continuously keep evolving and moving.', '"Feel,Moving,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I just want to try writing for other people \'cause it\'s quite exciting.', '"People,Try,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I\'ve been listening to a lot of music by Arca.', '"Music,Listening,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I get bored of music really easily, so I always try and make music that makes sense, but then it\'s just a little bit wrong."', '"Music,Always,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I struggled with the pressure of having the successful record after the first record. Second album syndrome. I\'m living proof; it\'s very real.', '"Pressure,Real,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Probably the No. 1 most important thing in my music is not to sound like anyone else. It is hard in this day and age.', '"Age,Music,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'A lot of electronic music out there feels cold. I want to incorporate a human element.', '"Music,Human,Cold"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I find that if I interact more, the crowd gets way more into the music. We also have a full live show happening, and I have lighting crew that travels around with me. We\'ve got this Infinity Prism thing, which is lots of fun. It\'s an optical illusion device that we carry around."', '"Music,Me,Illusion"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I love working with people and having them bring something to the table that I couldn\'t. I think one of my favourite artists to work with has been Kucka. She\'s Australian, too, and it\'s great working with her because we kind of have a very similar take on music, and we like a lot of the same stuff. We\'re not super-precious about ideas."', '"Love,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I was nine, and I was shopping in a supermarket with my dad. There was this cereal, and it had a special promotion with a CD inside the box that had a really simple music-making program on it. I got it, and that opened my mind to being able to make music on a computer and seeing all the different layers."', '"Music,Dad,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'The goal was always to do something that felt human but was 100 percent electronic.', '"Always,Human,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I actually found not having a routine was inspiration.', '"Routine,Inspiration,Found"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Often, when I work with a vocalist, I like to focus on the melodies first."', '"Work,Focus,First"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I definitely wanted the second record to be a much more grandiose thing. I wanted to push myself and make a big statement.', '"Myself,Big,Push"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Honestly, production when you first start can be difficult to wrap your head around."', '"Difficult,Start,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I want to make music that is completely electronic but doesn\'t feel it.', '"Music,Feel,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Sydney\'s beautiful, the weather\'s great, and the air\'s fresh and clean, but it doesn\'t have the scene and the amount of likeminded people. At home, things are very comfortable, but I feel like putting myself out there a bit."', '"Home,Great,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I don\'t think I make dance music. It\'s not even 4/4. And it\'s slow.', '"Music,Dance,Slow"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I never expected to make a lot of money from music.', '"Money,Music,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'It was a difficult second record. I had moments where I couldn\'t write; had moments where I was writing lots. It was just a massive learning process for me.', '"Learning,Me,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I had an idea when I was 18 or 19 to start tutoring people, like the way that people get tutored in saxophone or guitar, but for production. I really enjoyed it, but I don\'t have time for that any more."', '"Time,Guitar,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('393999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I think it would be nice to see more of an open culture to different music.', '"Music,Culture,See"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I\'ve never worked with huge pop acts, I mightn\'t like it, but it\'s something I\'ve always wanted to try."', '"Never,Always,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I used to never feel pressure to be creative; it\'s always just been a fun thing. And then suddenly, it\'s my job, and people are asking, \'Where\'s the record?\'"', '"Fun,Feel,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I want to keep Flume kind of experimental, weird, melodic, pretty."', '"Weird,Pretty,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I like bangers and really testosterone-fueled stuff.', '"Like,Really,Stuff"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Once I\'m in a situation where I can not do anything for three years and go off the map, I\'ll focus more on writing. Right now, I want to just make Flume awesome... and big."', '"Focus,Situation,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"To me it\'s all about textures, and that\'s the side of music that I\'m finding really exciting. I feel like it\'s one of the only parts of music that mankind hasn\'t fully discovered yet."', '"Music,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I just want to write another record that\'s as good or better than the one I\'ve already made. That\'s my main goal, to follow up stronger than before."', '"Good,Better,Stronger"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I\'m not into the attention thing so much.', '"Attention,Much,Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I feel like I\'ve got a pretty good presence online through Instagram and Facebook. I just keep it simple.', '"Good,Simple,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I love heavy music. I keep Flume nice and melodic, so I save the angry, testosterone-fueled heavy stuff for What So Not. I think it\'s a good defining thing for the two projects."', '"Love,Good,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"What So Not used to be a lot more dance-y, and now it\'s becoming a lot more melodic. Flume has always had that melodic thing, but it\'s starting to become a bit heavier, so it\'s just difficult to navigate between the two."', '"Difficult,Always,More"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I wanna make weird stuff.', '"Weird,Wanna,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I feel like I ask people who have been in the industry for a while a lot of questions.', '"Feel,People,Questions"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'Meditation is a really powerful tool I have for life now. The only reason I know about it is because I was stressing about writing and a friend taught me it. It\'s been useful.', '"Life,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'There\'s no person I aspire to be. I\'m just doing my own thing and seeing what happens - not looking to something and trying to be that.', '"Looking,Person,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"Music is a job, but I figured out ways to get my mind into a place where I could be creative. I actually discovered meditation. It enabled me to clear my mind of all the drama and focus on the music."', '"Music,Focus,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I don\'t mind playing my music live. It\'s fun. But what my real passion is is writing music.', '"Music,Passion,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', 'I had this little Bon Iver phase a few years back; \'Flume\' was one of my favourite songs.', '"Back,Phase,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"On stage, I like to dress up a bit. I\'m not scared to be like a character up there."', '"Character,Dress,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I can\'t sing, but I\'ll sing over this chord progression, like, over and over, for however long it takes - sometimes it\'s, like, two minutes, sometimes it\'s 20 minutes - until I\'ve found like a hook or something that I\'m really happy with. And then, basically, it just like that\'s my melody, and that\'s where I start from."', '"Long,Start,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd81', '"I like pop music, and I like really weird, strange stuff. It just didn\'t feel like there was anyone doing both."', '"Music,Feel,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"It\'s okay to not be working all the time and to be gentle on yourself when you\'re not. When it feels like you\'re losing that inspiration - or you\'re in a rut, not making stuff, and your head gets all weird - be gentle on yourself. Just ease into things naturally. But you still have to ease into it: you still have to sit in the chair."', '"Time,Yourself,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"The first beat that I ever made that I thought was actually worth a damn was called \'Toilet Paper Nostrils,\' and I made it when I had a cold. I had the worst cold ever. And I had toilet-paper nostrils making music, but it was really reflective of how I felt. It was a really sad trumpet sound."', '"Sad,Music,Worst"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"If I see a cop, it\'s not like, \'Oh, there\'s a cop who\'s gonna keep me safe.\' It\'s more, \'There\'s a cop who might be having a bad day, so don\'t make eye contact.\'"', '"Me,Day,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"We\'re all trying so hard to be beautiful, but the people in \'Kuso\' are trying so hard to be disgusting."', '"Beautiful,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I love my Fender Rhodes. It\'s been a part of my family since that keyboard came out, and I\'ve had it reworked so that it\'s in the best condition it\'s actually ever been in. That is my baby."', '"Love,Best,Family"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I believe there\'s more than this - that maybe, when we die, our brains conjure up some kind of shutdown experience, and that\'s what people try to sum up as the afterlife."', '"Experience,Believe,Die"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I grew up in the San Fernando Valley, which doesn\'t feel like L.A. It\'s a bit different. It\'s still L.A. County, but it\'s not the same, it\'s not the kind of place where they embrace you for being a weirdo. You were just left alone with your Nintendo, and that was my life."', '"Life,Alone,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I like to stay in the space of creativity, and I want to go towards that all the time."', '"Space,Time,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I like Philip Glass. I think he\'s made some really great contributions to his field. I love his style of playing - it\'s very loop-style.', '"Love,Great,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'Dilla could flip a boring record and make you feel like you were flying.', '"Boring,Feel,Flying"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I feel like my music has a reputation for being pretty serious or whatnot, but I like having fun."', '"Music,Fun,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I played saxophone for a while when I was a kid.', '"Saxophone,Kid,While"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"When I was in middle school, that\'s when I first started making beats. I was maybe 14, 16, something like that."', '"School,First,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'m just a fan of art and culture.', '"Art,Culture,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I never leave L.A. for too long. I\'m not one of those that go on a tour of the whole world. I probably should be, but I\'m not."', '"World,Long,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'There are things I\'ve seen and experienced in this world - things they don\'t talk about in too many books.', '"World,Talk,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I don\'t sit around listening to beats all day. There\'s so many producers, and so much of it is derivative."', '"Day,Listening,Sit"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'Sometimes I feel evil!', '"Feel,Sometimes,Evil"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I first was introduced to really, I guess, underground electronic music when I was in middle school."', '"Music,School,First"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"When I got into music, that was another way to be by myself."', '"Music,Myself,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I love Dilla, and who knows where this beat thing would be without him."', '"Love,Beat,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'m so thankful that I had music to turn to in the dark times and be able to understand myself through it.', '"Music,Thankful,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I took to the synthesizer. My cousin had some synthesizers, and I\'d always make stuff on those things."', '"Always,Things,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'Thundercat put me on to George Duke.', '"Me,Duke,Put"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"If I have to be \'the experimental guy\' or whatever, then I\'ll roll with it."', '"Whatever,Guy,Roll"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'m not the kind of person who\'s always out at the club if I don\'t have to be. I like chilling. I think that comes across in my music.', '"Music,Person,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Thundercat, specifically, is insane. I\'m always surprised at the things he comes up with when we\'re jamming out together. I gotta try to keep up with him and his ideas, be able to respond without speaking, and come through with some more music. He challenges me to keep it musical and not so computer."', '"Music,Together,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I definitely learned to communicate with other musicians better. I used to feel so intimidated by guys who can read notes, like, \'Oh my God, they\'re gonna think I\'m not even gonna be able to sit at the table.\' But I\'ve come to see that a lot of these musicians don\'t know how to read music either, and that made me feel good."', '"God,Good,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I wouldn\'t want to get involved with a game that\'s a stinker - I can smell one of those a mile away.', '"Game,Smell,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I know what it\'s like listening to Aphex Twin driving down the beach.', '"Listening,Know,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I\'m a geek, man."', '"Man,Geek"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I had the whole \'Ghostbusters\' toy set with the firehouse and the car and everything. Sometimes I\'d use my grandpa\'s camera and make little stop-motion cartoons with those toys - I was definitely a weird kid.', '"Car,Cartoons,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I actually really liked the music to the \'Friday the 13th\' Nintendo game. I still listen to it all the time. I sampled it in a couple records, too. It\'s hypnotic and dark but also really pretty."', '"Time,Music,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I was a real big fan of Lil Wayne when he first came out.', '"Real,Big,Big Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"In high school, I was that guy who was trying to be cool with everybody, but I never really had a core group of friends."', '"Cool,School,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"If I work with Bjork, then I\'ll be a happy soul, man."', '"Work,Man,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '\'Cosmogramma\' is basically the studies that map out the universe and the relations of heaven and hell.', '"Hell,Universe,Heaven"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I don\'t want to do one of those records where it\'s like a compilation of a bunch of all sorts of rappers on my beats. I don\'t find those to be focused albums.', '"Find,Want,Beats"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"It\'s tough when you\'re an artist because you get to go around the world and make a lot of friends, but guess what? One day, all these people that you love are going to die, from DJ Mehdi to DJ Dusk to J Dilla to Austin Peralta to DJ Rashad."', '"Love,World,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'All of the Flying Lotus records are exploring similar themes: These questions in my mind about what\'s next and what\'s beyond.', '"Mind,Questions,Beyond"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'Reading music has opened up me up so much. I\'ve been experimenting for so long and trying to make sense of things just from my ears. It takes forever. Now I can get where I want much quicker.', '"Music,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I do think your environment really plays into how you create. I lived in San Francisco for a bit, and I felt like I lived in the Matrix - so my music had that paranoid-of-the-outside sound to it."', '"Music,Create,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I don\'t like to brag about it, but there are people I\'ve worked with at the start of their career, and they\'ve all become very, very successful."', '"People,Start,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'George Clinton is the best storyteller in the world.', '"Best,World,Storyteller"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Before I started Brainfeeder, there were rumblings in our own circle about creating a label for us all. Then I started to see all these other ones from Europe try to capitalise on the scene. It didn\'t make sense to me that there were all these people who were trying to build on something that was in our backyard."', '"Me,People,Circle"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'People don\'t really care to be around you when you\'re going through tough times.', '"Care,Tough,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'People are not able to just make music anymore; we have to do things that don\'t necessarily make the art any better. But that\'s just how it is.', '"Art,Music,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'The Internet makes it possible for everyone to collaborate.', '"Internet,Possible,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I\'m really grateful for all of the things I\'ve had to learn along the way, you know? I don\'t know if I would want to say anything to my younger self. That way, you know, it really means something. If you have to go through it all, it really means something."', '"Grateful,Way,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'Kendrick is a true genius artist.', '"True,Genius,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'The producer role attracts introverts. Making music on your computer is so appealing to someone who just sits in their room all day.', '"Music,Day,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"When it comes to art in general now, we\'ve become so aware of our influence. We know when people are listening, when people are watching. It\'s not healthy. We start creating with that in the background of our mind. I think it\'s ruined my mind."', '"Art,Mind,Influence"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"With every album that I do, I try to feature a new instrument or sound."', '"New,Sound,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I don\'t have a great story, but I love Boards of Canada. I didn\'t get into it when it was happening; I got into it later on."', '"Love,Great,Canada"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I feel like part of my journey as a filmmaker is to tell different stories, whether they are just a black perspective on things that aren\'t necessarily hood movies, or Tyler Perry movies or Ava DuVernay movies. Love all those people, but that whole thing has been sowed up already."', '"Love,Movies,Journey"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I get homesick driving to the grocery store.', '"Driving,Get,Grocery"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I found so many reasons to call it \'You\'re Dead!\' - not just because I wanted to make this album about the journey through death. I was watching the music scene that I came up with kind of go stale and watching the lights go out on a lot of my friends.', '"Death,Music,Journey"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"The Soft Machine\'s \'Volume Two\' inspired me heavily. That record just feels like it was all done in the same breath. It\'s genius, and it\'s silly at times. But I love the fact that every time I listen to it, I listen from the beginning and want to play it out."', '"Love,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I was first inspired to make music by my cousin Oran. He was making music on an old Mac II by himself in his little lab, and I just started taking up after him. He was the first person to put a machine in front of me to work on. He was like my big brother, someone who I looked up to."', '"Work,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I wish I could write music notation. Even if I couldn\'t play it, I wish I could just write it."', '"Music,Wish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"When I made \'1983,\' there were a bunch of tracks that were in the early drafts that didn\'t make it because they just sounded like tracks for rappers, and that\'s not really the sound I look for when I produce my own albums."', '"Look,My Own,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"A strong concept is the most important thing in creating a record. When you can listen to it and see a whole movie in your head, that\'s what separates an instrumental album from a beat tape."', '"Important,See,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Before saying, \'This track is so dope; it\'s gonna go on the album,\' I like to take some time away from it and see how I feel about it in a few months. If it\'s gonna get released, I gotta love it - it\'s gonna have my name on it forever."', '"Love,Time,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I\'m not much of a coffee person, but when I wake up and the sun is shining through the window, I\'ll get a lil\' bit of green tea and get to work."', '"Work,Green,Window"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"It\'s the old-school jazz mentality that I connect with the most. I dig the idea of the seeker, the guy who\'s always trying to figure out why he is doing music and trying to understand and make sense of his instrument in a world which deals with rigid instruction."', '"Music,World,Jazz"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Part of what I like to do with Brainfeeder is to get the younger kids hearing jazz, because they don\'t know where to go to really hear it. Brainfeeder gives me a platform to put out people like Kamasi Washington or Austin Peralta."', '"Me,Jazz,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I love Snoop - I grew up with his music - but I never thought for a second that we\'d work together.', '"Love,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Death is a reality, and one day I\'m not going to be here anymore, and whatever\'s next might not be that bad either."', '"Death,Reality,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I always feel like the past informs my present musically.', '"Past,Feel,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I am a big cinema nerd! I\'ve absorbed a lot of films.', '"Cinema,I Am,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Takashi Miike is definitely one of my top five, you know?"', '"Know,Top,Five"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'d love to work with Drake. I got Drake beats.', '"Love,Work,Beats"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I just understand that I\'m supposed to be one of those people that disrupts the flavor a little bit instead of being part of the same sound as everyone else.', '"People,Sound,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I like comedy.', '"Comedy,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'m a silly guy.', '"Guy,Silly"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'ve been working with Thundercat forever.', '"Forever,Been,Working"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'My music divides people!', '"Music,People,Divides"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Childish Gambino - him and I are the same age, and I really like him."', '"Age,Childish,Same"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I like boring. Boring is cool.', '"Cool,Boring,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I\'m the kind of person who needs to be challenged all the time. I need my brain to go, or else I just end up playing video games all day, you know? That\'s cool too, I guess, at times."', '"Cool,Time,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'m always seeing stuff and imagining scenes in my head when I\'m making music.', '"Music,Always,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I can\'t let darkness be what guides my decisions. I can\'t let that be what guides how I treat people. I can\'t let that be what drives my art, either."', '"Art,Darkness,Treat"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I was 10 years old when the Northridge quake happened, and I lived right in the area, so it was a traumatic thing for me. I\'d never had anything like that happen before. It\'s always stuck with me."', '"Me,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I love \'Pop Team Epic,\' which is really trippy."', '"Love,Team,Epic"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I go through phases when I\'m super into my anime stuff.', '"Go,Through,Anime"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'My collaborations tend to be pretty organic. It starts off with me being a fan first.', '"Me,Organic,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Whenever I am making stuff, I got a thing in the back of my mind: \'Oh, this would be so perfect for\' whoever."', '"Mind,I Am,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I need to help people to create the best work that they can. It\'s just something a producer should do anyway.', '"Work,Best,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I\'ve always been a techie kind of person.', '"Person,Always,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I built computers and stuff when I was a teenager and whatever.', '"Computers,Whatever,Stuff"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I decided to play the saxophone because it was the most obvious instrument in my family. There were a lot of saxophone players in my family, and there were extra saxophones, so that was an easy one to pick up. It was fun - it was okay - it just wasn\'t me. It didn\'t feel like my instrument, so I never followed through."', '"Family,Me,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I had a little Walkman, the worst Walkman ever. It was the yellow one, that underwater Walkman. Like you need to take a Walkman under water."', '"Water,Underwater,Worst"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Truth be told, I think jazz is a mind-set. It\'s not necessarily, like, this guy picked up a horn and did this or whatever."', '"Truth,Jazz,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I go through phases where I\'m not into jazz as much, and then I\'ll get heavy, heavy, heavy into it."', '"Jazz,Go,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"For me, being 10 years old and seeing \'Jurassic Park\' for the first time blew my mind. I want music to feel like that."', '"Time,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'When I can make music and don\'t have to think about anyone else\'s ideas or voice - when I\'m making something that only I can make - it feels good. It\'s nice when you can find a sound that only you can make. No one else can make \'Cosmogramma.\' No one else can make \'Until the Quiet Comes.\'', '"Good,Music,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I remember Usher came up to me at Coachella once, and it\'s like, \'Are you sure you\'re talking to the right person? How do you even know what I look like? You\'re not supposed to know who I am.\'"', '"Look,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', 'I work a lot.', '"Work,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"I like when my mind is being stimulated and challenged, and I\'m forced to be creative."', '"Mind,Creative,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd82', '"Whenever it gets a little cold in L.A., it gives me an excuse to light my fireplace. You could stare at that joint for, like, a cool two hours. It\'s entrancing."', '"Cool,Me,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd83', '"I never went to a university, and I am proud to say so because I don\'t think I have done too badly."', '"I Am,Done,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd83', '"I told as much of my life as I could to encourage people: to encourage others to get to where they should be, where they want to be."', '"Life,My Life,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'Keep your temper. A decision made in anger is never sound.', '"Anger,Decision,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'Keep your eye on the ball.', '"Your,Ball,Eye"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', '"Take pride in your work at all times. Remember, respect for an umpire is created off the field as well as on."', '"Work,Respect,Pride"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'Hear only the things you should hear - be deaf to others.', '"Deaf,Others,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'Keep all your personalities out of your work. Forget and forgive.', '"Work,Forget,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'Avoid sarcasm. Don\'t insist on the last word.', '"Sarcasm,Avoid,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', 'I\'d hate this to get out but I really like opera.', '"Hate,Opera,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', '"Review your work. You will find, if you are honest, that 90% of the trouble is traceable to loafing."', '"Work,Will,Review"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd85', '"Never charge a player and, above all, no pointing your finger or yelling."', '"Never,Your,Above"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Stereotypes do exist, but we have to walk through them."', '"Walk,Stereotypes,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I think \'The Color of Money\' was very instrumental in opening up other opportunities. People started to recognize me as an artist after that film. And then, after I did \'Bird,\' it was more solidified."', '"Money,Bird,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"My wife is completely different from me: she\'s good with everyone, whereas I\'m good at directed conversation when I have a purpose for it, like now. If everyone\'s sitting around being social, I\'m not great."', '"Good,Great,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"When children and youth are deprived of their right to education, their community is deprived of a sustainable future. It is all the more true with refugees."', '"Education,Future,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"We\'re supposed to be an example of freedom, and if we are doing things that are injustice to people, then what is our statement?"', '"Freedom,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"My eye? It\'s a genetic thing. My dad had it, and now I have it. You know, I just found out that it may be correctable a little bit, because it does impair my vision. When I look up, I lose sight in this eye. I think, maybe for other people, it informs the way they see me."', '"Dad,Vision,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"As human beings, we all have reasons for our behavior. There may be people who have certain physiological issues that dictate why they make certain choices. On the whole, though, I think we\'re dictated by our structure, our past, our environment, our culture. So once you understand the patterns that shape a person, how can you not find sympathy?"', '"Sympathy,Culture,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"The key is that I\'m trying to keep growing and trying to keep learning and deepen my connection in every way, in my life, in my work. That\'s what I do when I look at a role."', '"Life,Work,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I\'ve had many incidents in my life of racism. I\'ve been thrown on the ground. I\'ve been frisked. I\'ve been arrested so many times I couldn\'t tell you. I have no need to talk about it.', '"Life,My Life,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"There\'s a molecule inside of you that is connected to everything - every person, every energy, every thing. You look for it, and when you find it, then you allow it to magnify and grow and be the dominating chemistry inside of you."', '"Look,Energy,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It\'s all about destiny. That\'s why people look at the zodiac or the I Ching - because there\'s a certain order to life, and that order has been lived since the beginning of time. No matter what you do, you\'re going to live inside of it."', '"Life,Time,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Our leaders must hear us speaking on behalf of our brothers and sisters in South Sudan. If the moral duty to save lives and work toward peace is not compelling enough to drive decision-makers, we must remind them that we care and will hold them accountable."', '"Work,Peace,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"While it\'s easy for South Sudan to feel distant, the situation is all too real for the South Sudanese mothers choosing which child gets to eat tomorrow. This is a time when we must look outward together and declare that humanity has no borders - no one deserves to suffer like this, especially in a world of such abundance."', '"Time,Together,Tomorrow"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"College football, acting, opera singing - I approached them all in the same obsessive way."', '"Football,Singing,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I\'ve been trying to understand conflict and violence ever since I was a kid. You know. There were a few things that happened even on my block - the Black Panthers used to be right around the corner from where we were.', '"Black,Conflict,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I am just back from South Sudan, one of the world\'s most fragile nations. For years, I have been moved by the kind people who maintain hope that they will live to see peace. My heart has ached for them, as they have endured pain and violence that make such hope feel out of reach."', '"Hope,Peace,Pain"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I love to play chess. The last time I was playing, I started to really see the board. I don\'t mean just seeing a few moves ahead - something else. My game started getting better. It\'s the patterns. The patterns are universal."', '"Love,Time,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It is possible for a kid from east Texas, raised in south central LA and Carson, who believes in his dreams, commits himself to them with his heart, to touch them and to have them happen."', '"Dreams,Heart,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"When I was a kid, the only way I saw movies was from the back seat of my family\'s car at the drive-in."', '"Family,Car,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"As an actor, I\'ve always wanted to do characters that would help me find my connection with others and connect all of us together. You always want the energy of the character, the spirit of the person, to enter you. I\'ve been doing this for 26 years and some of the things I\'ve done are always with me."', '"Together,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I can play a man who\'s despicable. But I\'ll still look inside him to find a point of connection. If I can find that kernel, audiences will relate to me."', '"Man,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I\'m an actor. And I guess I\'ve done so many movies I\'ve achieved some high visibility. But a star? I guess I still think of myself as kind of a worker ant.', '"Movies,Myself,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"In a lot of films, they\'re showing more complete, developed characters of diverse ethnic backgrounds. The larger concern is to be able to tastefully explore the stereotypes, and still move past them to see the core of people."', '"Past,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I care about people. In the end, I think they feel it. It comes across, regardless of the character I\'m portraying."', '"Character,Care,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I really wasn\'t even sure if I should continue acting. I would like try and figure out if I could be good enough to do it. It was like 10 or 12 years into my career before I felt like maybe I can do it. It was such a different time than now.', '"Time,Good,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I think I didn\'t know whether I wanted to keep acting deep into my career. I kept trying to see if I would be able to do it well enough to make that part of my destiny or part of what I was supposed to do.', '"Destiny,Acting,See"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I liked \'Star Wars\' as a kid. I liked science fiction.', '"Science,Science Fiction,Star"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I always stand up for what I believe and what I want to.', '"Believe,Stand,Stand Up"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I was asked if I would play President Obama in \'My Name is Khan.\' I didn\'t feel comfortable with doing it. Partly because he was still in office, but mainly because I felt that there were other people who were better suited to doing the role."', '"Better,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I can\'t say I follow it, but I\'ve watched \'Downton Abbey\' a couple of times and loved it."', '"Follow,Loved,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Poitier opened the doors to so many artists, not just black artists. There is a line that goes from black to Latin to Asian with regards to roles."', '"Black,Doors,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"If there is inequality, and that equates with colour, then I\'m going to deal with it."', '"Inequality,Colour,Deal"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"The first time I ever went out of the country, it was to London. I was with the choir from my college, and we were touring around all these different churches. I loved it so much I tried to find a way to stay there."', '"Time,Way,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'May we remain connected in love. We are one.', '"Love,Connected,May"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"You have to ask if the country would have been ready for Barack Obama if we hadn\'t been prepared by Colin Powell and Condoleezza Rice. If they hadn\'t already been in positions of enormous power and influence - secretary of state, secretary of defence - you know what I mean?"', '"Power,Influence,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I\'d spend every summer in Longview on my grandfather\'s farm. It was a tiny little town divided by a river, which was the segregation line: that side white, this side black. And meanwhile, I lived in Compton - basically, another whole world sealed into 10 square blocks. It\'s interesting how insular an environment can be."', '"Black,River,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"You try to pull away the experiences until you get to the core of humanity, and you find that light that exists in everybody. It\'s that light that I\'m searching for in all of my work - is that connective thing, that ether that enters all of us - you know what I mean? That\'s a part of God."', '"Work,God,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I try to live my life in a holistic way, show that all of it intersects because I\'m coming from the same place. Now, at the core of it, I\'m just trying to connect and be there, so I\'m trying to be there for my family, my wife, my kids, my friends."', '"Life,Family,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I stay true because whatever the project is, I\'m still looking for inside of that character. It\'s the thing that connects him to me and to everybody else. So, the search is the same. It\'s to unveil the truth, and that\'s how I stay true, because my purpose isn\'t altered."', '"Truth,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"In life, there\'s a ladder sometimes, and maybe at the top, there\'s a mirror. You take a step up, then maybe three steps down... just because you don\'t want to face the decloaking in the mirror."', '"Life,Mirror,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It\'s a contract of connection to be in the same space and watch and listen to stories and be caught in them. When you\'re in a theater, your brain expands because somebody in the theater may do something or respond to something that you wouldn\'t have."', '"Space,Brain,Connection"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I submerged myself in all the information that I could find about Idi Amin. I mean, before I left Los Angeles, I was studying Kiswahili. I was working on the dialect. I was studying every documentary and tape of him that I could find - not just visual, but also audiocassettes, even in other languages when he was speaking in other dialects."', '"Myself,Information,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I had been playing really interesting roles before I got great roles. Little ones - \'The Crying Game\' I loved working on, and then \'Bird,\' \'Ghost Dog,\' so many films."', '"Great,Bird,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It\'s hard for me to judge my own films as an artist sometimes. But as an artist, I did feel a fulfillment working on them, you know?"', '"Me,Feel,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I think I\'ve made some choices that maybe I wasn\'t so sure about for some reason or another. But I\'m one of the lucky ones. Even when I was young, I played Bird, and that\'s a role people wait for their whole lifetime."', '"Bird,Wait,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I\'m always surprised when an actor goes so deeply into the truth that they shake you to your core.', '"Truth,Always,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Ultimately, all human beings fulfill their patterns. We\'re set in a certain archetype, and we fulfill that destiny."', '"Destiny,Human,Patterns"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"If I go to a reunion in east Texas, my mother\'s side or my father\'s, one out of ten is a preacher or a teacher. That\'s just the way it is in my family."', '"Family,Teacher,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'Good science fiction is always based in contemporary truths.', '"Science,Good,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I think the only consistent thing is that I like projects that explore different social themes. \'Our Family Wedding\' is a comedy, but it deals with two different cultures coming together. It\'s also about people letting go."', '"Family,Wedding,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Until film is just as easily accessible as a pen or pencil, then it\'s not completely an art form. In painting, you can just pick up a piece of chalk, a stick, or whatever. In sculpture, you can get a rock. Writing, you just need a pencil and paper. Film has been a very elitist medium. It costs so much money."', '"Money,Art,Painting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I\'m inspired to work with good actors, period. I want to work with the best anytime because I think they\'ll make me better."', '"Work,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"To try and act like we haven\'t had great progress is not true. Obama didn\'t fail - he changed the psyche of the nation and, in some ways, the world."', '"Great,Progress,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'It\'s tough when you have to be away. But I\'m probably at home more than my dad was because he was working two or three jobs sometimes.', '"Home,Dad,Tough"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"My wife, Keisha, came home once, and I had these violinists playing for her, and I\'d prepared dinner for her, and I write poems. She\'s pretty amazing, so I like to celebrate that. She\'s really taught me how to celebrate life; that\'s something I\'ve learned."', '"Life,Home,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"On the whole, I now see my work as being an expression of my spiritual life and, because I look at it that way, I have a different centre. I go through the stress and pressure, but I think I\'m lucky because I come from a different source point."', '"Life,Work,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I\'ve been fortunate, I guess: I\'ve gotten to play a lot of very diverse roles for quite a long time. But in the beginning, I was thinking, \'I\'m not gonna do certain characters. I will be willing to say no and live on a couch.\' And I was really happy."', '"Time,Thinking,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I fell through a stage once. I was doing a truly African dance, and all of a sudden, I hit the ground with my foot and went straight through the stage. I guess they didn\'t have much money, so the floor was kind of rotting."', '"Money,Dance,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It\'s abhorrent to me that somebody is just evil, and you can\'t explain it."', '"Me,Evil,Explain"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I\'m fascinated by the capacity to be able to do harm. I struggle every day with the ability of people to do evil. Not just the big things - the petty things that people do in order to make someone feel small, when it\'s so easy to do, and it hurts so much."', '"Struggle,Day,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I put down the camera long ago, you know? I was here in London, aged 19, and I was obsessed with my camera, shooting everything I could. Then someone stole it. It helped me to see things for the first time."', '"Time,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I always try to remain aware that what affects others affects me, too."', '"Me,Always,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I\'d been reading Eastern philosophy since I was a kid. And I meditated. I did it on a daily basis. It\'s the one thing I do with any consistency. Meditation gives you a different kind of mindset. It\'s very powerful.', '"Daily,Consistency,Mindset"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', 'I was a curious child. I\'d debate with anyone who came to the door - people from the Islamic community... Jehovah\'s Witnesses... anyone.', '"Community,Debate,Door"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Fame allows you a lot of opportunities to experience new things and connect with people. But on the other hand, people\'s perceptions of you can limit the scope of your relationships with them. You walk both lines."', '"Experience,Walk,New"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"The Internet is part of our evolution. The mystics used to say, \'We can travel across the planet in a thought.\' Now we really can. We can be connected with a million people at a time."', '"Time,Travel,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I want a director who can let me feel that he\'s listening and watching and that he\'s got me covered. That security is really important for me because sometimes you go into a vulnerable space, and you want to be able to look to somebody because you get insecure: \'Did I do that right?\'"', '"Space,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Look - I\'m an African-American. I\'m black. But I\'m just looking at the character and trying to find his soul, his energy. If you can wipe away the blanket of skin and flesh that people tend to see, and look inside for the essence of the soul, then that\'s the work I\'m doing. That\'s the work I always do."', '"Work,Black,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I want to get better as an actor, to keep trying to work harder, trying to discover something different. In some ways, it\'s a pretty frightening experience. But normally, I do tend to walk against fear and hope that I\'ll be able to survive."', '"Work,Hope,Experience"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It\'s important for youth, black youths particularly, to be able to fill in the blanks of themselves so they can know completely who they are, but also all the country to understand what this means: what the civil rights movement does to us as people. It is part of the journey that we must be on in order to become fully evolved human beings."', '"Journey,Youth,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I try to be like a forest, revitalizing and constantly growing... Kids would tease me, calling me \'Little Bush.\' But... I thought being called Forest helped me find my identity."', '"Me,Identity,Forest"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I go back and forth between indie and studio because I feel like it, not because I feel obligated to do one or the other."', '"Feel,Back,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"In high school, I did some musicals, but I never took acting until college. I was studying opera, classical voice, and a speech teacher asked me to audition for this play, and I got the lead."', '"Teacher,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Directing is more comfortable for me because, as an actor, there\'s always something inherently false. Because I\'m not that person."', '"Me,Person,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"It rests in the hands of the common person as well as those with the power to shape humanity\'s course toward a world where every child, woman and man\'s most basic needs are met."', '"Power,Man,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"When we talk about the issue of child soldiers, it can be easy to focus just on ending recruitment and liberating those boys and girls who are currently being held in military camps. Obviously, both of these are incredibly important goals, but it\'s also essential that we not forget about former child soldiers once they are liberated."', '"Focus,Goals,Ending"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"In some sense, when you take a child soldier out of an armed group, you\'ve taken away the identity he or she has had for years, and you can\'t assume life is just going to return to normal."', '"Life,Identity,Soldier"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"For many child soldiers, war and violence are all they have ever known. If we don\'t take it upon ourselves to show them an alternative, then they\'re going to be soldiers forever, and they\'ll continue to be recruited and to participate in violence if another conflict starts five or 10 years down the road."', '"War,Road,Conflict"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I was in middle school right around the time the Bloods and the Crips started taking root in Compton and a lot of the other neighborhoods around me. I saw way too many of my peers - smart, kind, good kids - who got drawn into gangs and violence, and their futures were going to be forever scarred by that."', '"Time,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Many of the wars we see around the world start as domestic conflicts that are fueled by external forces and powers. My view is that we can help peace if we help communities transform from the inside, on their own terms."', '"Peace,View,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"The characters I\'ve portrayed may outwardly be quite different from one another, but I\'ve found that they\'re also intrinsically linked."', '"May,Quite,Found"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I think that cinema and the arts are central in our lives because we grow up and learn about the world through our exposure to stories. Parents use them as a tool to teach their children fundamental truths and values, much as adults can view them to gain exposure to cultures and individuals that they\'d never be able to view in their own lives."', '"View,Cinema,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"Cinema and the arts invite viewers to focus on a story and, in doing so, peel away its layers and peer into the depths of the human soul."', '"Focus,Soul,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I try to support stories that enable us to see the difficulties in our society and the challenges we face, which is why I\'ve also produced documentaries like \'Brick City\' and \'Serving Life.\'"', '"Life,Society,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd86', '"I see a deep connection between peace and change: peace always starts from within, for communities and people alike. The same is true of change: real change starts from within."', '"Change,Peace,True"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd87', '"I work as if I were going to be the next person to need a respirator. I share in the benefits I bestow on others, and my work has enriched my life."', '"Life,Work,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd87', '"My daddy was a World War I pilot, and I just wanted to be able to fly like he did."', '"War,Fly,World"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd87', '"In the human lung, there are millions of air foils, just like aeroplane wings, which facilitate normal breathing."', '"Wings,Air,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I live the perfect life.', '"Life,Perfect,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Time catches everyone. Sooner or later, it gets everybody."', '"Time,Everyone,Sooner Or Later"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I feel bad for guys in other sports that never work a job. Think about it, most MMA fighters have had to do something for money whereas a guy who was an athlete in college sport then went straight to the pros, he\'s never had a skill outside of sport."', '"Work,Money,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I like deer. They\'re kinda cool.', '"Cool,Deer,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Thiago Santos is a guy who can take your belt from you with one punch.', '"Your,Punch,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I was a police officer in Augusta, Ga."', '"Police,Police Officer,Officer"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"You have to move on with your life at some point. You don\'t quit fighting, fighting quits you at some point. It\'s very unfortunate, but that\'s the nature of the beast. And that\'s one of those things, too, that I like to tell young fighters. Have a backup plan."', '"Life,Nature,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I try to break a sweat every day doing something. Try to do hot pilates once a week. I\'m not kidding. I actually hurt myself doing hot pilates, so I got that going for me."', '"Myself,Sweat,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"People think TRT is for lazy people. No, it\'s just you\'re just trying to improve yourself."', '"Yourself,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"For like a year, even after I retired, my ear would just bleed. There was just some scar tissue on it that tore open so many times that it just started bleeding all the time. It\'s rough on the wife, she has to keep washing the sheets again and again."', '"Time,Wife,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'You would have to be born with a gene that doesn\'t allow you to recognize sarcasm if you take anything I say seriously.', '"Sarcasm,Born,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I love football and basketball but fighting is the original, most primitive to our nature."', '"Love,Nature,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I try not to make personal attacks on people - unless they\'re deserving.', '"People,Try,Personal"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"We grew up in an era where there was a lot of fear of HIV. Everybody worried about it and everybody took precautions, and everybody knew that it was a thing that was out there. As it slowed down, it left the spotlight, people forgot."', '"Fear,People,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"During a fight with Anderson Silva, I slipped on an imaginary banana peel."', '"Fight,Banana,Imaginary"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Me and my step-dad shared a $500 Chevy Celebrity, a 1983 Dodge Ram truck, and an old Ford Ranger truck - it was a piece of junk. I hated that thing. It fell apart. It didn\'t always go in reverse. So I drove in a circle or I would just get somebody to sit in the thing and I would push it backward."', '"Me,Circle,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"There are two things I want to be able to know when I walk into a fight, or with anything in life. And I\'m not Superman, I\'m not even that great at fighting. Those two things are: I have done everything in my power to prepare for this and I will not quit, no matter what."', '"Life,Power,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I do actually enjoy the process of putting my thoughts down on paper and having people actually read them.', '"Thoughts,Process,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"It gets old, all of it. People putting a lot of hopes and dreams on you. Telling you they put money on you, and \'you\'re my kid\'s idol.\'"', '"Dreams,Money,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I wrote an article for Revolver and it was very offensive.', '"Article,Offensive,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Taking care of your family is the manliest thing you can do.', '"Family,Care,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'It\'s very unmanly to change yourself for others. Be comfortable with oneself. There have been feminist movements but there\'s never been a male one.', '"Change,Yourself,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I can do anything for 25 minutes.', '"I Can,Anything,Minutes"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'What\'s wrong with wanting to be better at your job?', '"Better,Wrong,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'ve always kind of been the guy next door who just happens to fight for a living. I tried to figure out what was special and marketable about me early on in my career and I realized that there\'s absolutely nothing special about me, so I wanted that."', '"Fight,Me,Door"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Unfortunately, I found out when I was trying to like square up with people and face off with people and, like, try to intimidate them and I\'m pretty non-threatening."', '"Face,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"HIV is not a gay or straight disease. It\'s a young people\'s disease, unfortunately."', '"Gay,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"When I announced my retirement, that was actually when I was trying to come back and I realized, it just wasn\'t viable. It passed me by. My shoulder is done. I brush my teeth with my left hand now. That\'s just the way it goes. I can\'t shoot a basketball, I can\'t throw any kind of ball. I was right handed."', '"Me,Way,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'You can\'t cuss on TV. It does hurt your brand if you do stuff like that. That\'s not what blue chip sponsors are looking for.', '"Blue,Looking,Hurt"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"It was weird, I saw the Brian Stann vs. Wanderlei fight, I thought, if I don\'t have another of those in me, there\'s no point in continuing. I never really cared about winning or losing, then don\'t put the product out there at all if it\'s going to be subpar."', '"Fight,Me,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"The biggest thing I learned is that when Dana says retire, you should retire. Otherwise, you will blow your knee out before your next fight."', '"Fight,Will,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Nobody goes, \'I\'m a top 10 fighter. Well, maybe Top 15. I can beat a lot of guys\'... Nobody ever says that. That\'s the thing with having a grasp on reality. I know I\'m not the best."', '"Best,Reality,Fighter"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I thought wrestling was the stuff where people jumped off ropes. So that was my experience with wrestling.', '"Experience,People,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I just love fighting. I know I\'m not the best, but I\'m still pretty good, there\'s a lot of people I can still beat. What do you do. What else am I supposed to do? I have no other skills. I enjoy doing this. There\'s nothing I\'d really rather do, you know?"', '"Love,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"In the grand scheme of things, fighting people in the cage is not that big of a deal, I know. It\'s not a hero profession even though its treated as one. It\'s not being a soldier or police officer or paramedic of firefighter or anything."', '"Hero,Police,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Every injury is specific to what has happened, but the advice that I will give is that if you have a lower body injury, to work your upper body out. If you have an upper body injury, work your lower body out. Again, move what is not broken and you will definitely feel better."', '"Work,Advice,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'My fitness philosophy is very different from the UFC fighter fitness philosophy. Mine is to work out in a way that you will be able to sustain for the next 20 years.', '"Work,Fitness,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'My philosophy when I trained was to be 1% better every day.', '"Day,Better,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I will give one piece of advice that always keeps me going; get your body moving every day, no matter what. Don\'t truly have an off day, just move. Move light and try to get your body moving to break a light sweat."', '"Sweat,Me,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I hate flying so I always drive.', '"Hate,Drive,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I like listening to Method Man before fighting.', '"Man,Fighting,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'The best car I ever had was a Mazda 626. I paid $72 for it. The guy told me if I towed it off his property I could do whatever I wanted to it. So I paid to have it towed to my house and me and my step-dad fixed it up and drove it until I totalled it.', '"Best,Car,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'m never going to struggle but I definitely want to make more money, we all do."', '"Money,Struggle,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I\'ve made a ton of money but I don\'t have as much as I\'d like.', '"Money,Like,Made"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I worked in a dining hall in college and I worked at UPS for a full three weeks - it was the worst job I ever had.', '"Worst,Three,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I\'m kind of a grinder.', '"Kind,Grinder"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I get to work out for my job and punch people and wrassle, that\'s a pretty cool job."', '"Cool,Work,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'ve framed houses, worked on an asphalt crew, I was a cop, a lifeguard."', '"Crew,Cop,Lifeguard"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'ve been victimized by general filthiness on multiple occasions... I received a nasty staph infection... I was told to wait it out... a few days later I literally thought I was going to die... I ended up being on antibiotics for five weeks and, as a result, I had to back out of the fight against Machida."', '"Fight,Wait,Result"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"You get away from something long enough, you miss it. You get hungry for it."', '"Long,Enough,Hungry"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'It\'s nice to get to do other things and not worry about fighting.', '"Fighting,Worry,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'m someone who needs goals and direction, and fighting provided that for me."', '"Me,Goals,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I remember being 32 years old and feeling great, better than ever physically. Then at 33, I tore my shoulder and was out for eight months, and it was like I fell off a cliff. I was never the same."', '"Great,Remember,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"You talk to people, and they don\'t understand our water. They come and turn on a tap and drink clean water, and to them, that\'s amazing. Millions of people around the world have to carry water miles and miles, and that\'s all they have. It\'s hard for fat Americans like myself to even understand that."', '"Amazing,Myself,Water"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"If it were up to me, I\'d be fighting chumps."', '"Me,Fighting,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"You have the belt, you fight who they tell you to fight."', '"Fight,Tell,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I am a Georgia guy, and I have Brett Favre\'s card when he played with the Atlanta Falcons. That\'s my retirement plan."', '"I Am,Retirement,Plan"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I really believe zombies are a threat to our national security.', '"Believe,Security,National Security"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Whatever Brett Favre does, it\'s a sign of the apocalypse."', '"Whatever,Sign,Apocalypse"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I grew up in a different era. People were definitely afraid of HIV back then, but education also helped change the way we thought about the disease. That education helped my generation make smarter choices about the way we protected ourselves."', '"Education,Change,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'It\'s long been a problem. But I\'m not just talking about the UFC - I mean homophobia in sports in general and athletes sometimes say really stupid things.', '"Sports,Stupid,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I think anyplace people can be themselves is a good thing.', '"Good,People,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Gay, straight, whatever - none of that actually matters when you\'re fighting someone. Not what you have in your bank account, what you drive, what sex you are, none of it. I think that\'s the message the UFC has been trying to push."', '"Sex,Drive,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Anytime you think about ring rust and travel and camps back-to-back, it helps not having any bad injuries and being able to train consistently."', '"Travel,Bad,Injuries"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"The only thing that gives my mom pleasure in life is buying stuff off QVC, and I\'m gonna pay those bills. I paid my mom\'s house off. My wife\'s family needs help? I\'m gonna take care of that."', '"Life,Family,Mom"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"It was so fun, 2006, 2007, 2008. I went into the gym and I felt like I was winning in the gym, which is important for an athlete."', '"Fun,Winning,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I\'m not a naturally giving person.', '"Person,Giving,Naturally"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I don\'t really give a damn about too much other than myself.', '"Myself,Damn,Too Much"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I found being a coach in \'The Ultimate Fighter\' series hard because I had to care about others. I don\'t feel a lot of empathy with others. Having kids is going to be a scary one for me - I guess I\'m going to have to learn.', '"Me,Empathy,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Anyone can get beaten in mixed martial arts. It\'s the nature of the sport.', '"Nature,Get,Anyone"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I have great coaches, but one thing I\'ve never really had is that head coach - a Greg Jackson, Matt Hume, John Hackleman."', '"Great,Never,Head"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I like to start every sentence with: \'So here\'s the deal.\'', '"Start,Deal,Here"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'There will be a time when I physically cannot do this sport.', '"Time,Will,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'m a nice guy. I\'m trying to be positive. I\'ve got my own things, I\'m kinda crazy but I\'m not trying to hurt anybody. I\'m trying to be good and I\'m doing the best I can. Just like everybody else."', '"Positive,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I don\'t think you should punish a guy for losing when they were hurt.', '"Losing,Hurt,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I want people to like me.', '"Me,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Some guys are real noble guys, like Rich Franklin or Randy Couture. These guys are just really good people who happen to fight."', '"Good,Fight,Good People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I hate when someone gets the better of me. A Division 1 wrestler comes in and takes me down and I get frustrated.', '"Hate,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I like to make people quit. Whether it\'s because I\'m striking them or submitting them, I just want to make them quit. In the war of wills, that\'s the win."', '"War,People,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I\'ve always mid-lined myself where I don\'t really expect myself to do big things or to win big fights. It\'s not a lack of confidence, it\'s just that I think to an extent that you need a bit of an ego if you\'re going to think that you\'re going to conquer something."', '"Myself,Confidence,Conquer"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I like ice cream, I don\'t like pain."', '"Pain,Ice Cream,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Winning the belt is one thing. But you\'re not really a champion until you defend it.', '"Champion,Winning,One Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"No, I don\'t play video games."', '"Video Games,Play,Video"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"In the beginning, fighting was fun - I wasn\'t concerned with the outcome. At some point, I started training out of fear and anger. I wasn\'t really happy."', '"Anger,Fear,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I\'m pretty careful not to make friends with other guys who fight at 205.', '"Fight,Careful,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I don\'t have the best chin in the world.', '"Best,World,Chin"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"When I know that I trained real hard and I had a good training camp, that\'s when I\'m very confident. But sometimes I don\'t train hard and I don\'t feel that confident."', '"Good,Training,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'I had some pretty substantial injuries.', '"Injuries,Pretty,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"The UFC actually does a lot of charity stuff, but they don\'t talk about it that much."', '"Talk,Charity,About"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"When you get the opportunity to give away somebody else\'s money to make somebody else\'s life a little better. That\'s pretty cool, actually."', '"Life,Cool,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I always wanted to work in charitable things, community outreach, etc."', '"Work,Community,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'If you look at UFC champions: BJ Penn - terrifying! GSP - terrifying! Anderson Silva - terrifying! But I\'m not terrifying.', '"Look,UFC,Champions"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I am not the super-submission guy, I am not the one-punch KO guy, so I am not the most feared guy in the world. But I will not quit, I will not break and I will fight you like a dog for every second of every round."', '"Fight,World,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I am not a super-talented guy, I\'m just a dude who will fight you tooth and nail."', '"Fight,I Am,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Jesus was a liberal. Jesus was like the original liberal.', '"Like,Liberal,Original"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I say whatever\'s on my mind, I don\'t really care."', '"Mind,Care,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'Look what happened when I fought Anderson Silva. It can\'t possibly get worse than that. I\'ve already seen the bottom and it wasn\'t that bad. I made it through. I survived. It\'s fighting. It\'s not the end of the world.', '"Look,World,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', 'It sucks when you do poorly at your job.', '"Job,Your,Sucks"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"Here\'s the deal: the extraordinary becomes ordinary really quickly. One minute, everything is new and amazing, the next it\'s expected."', '"Amazing,New,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd88', '"I like not having a job, not having to get up early in the morning is awesome. I would recommend it to anybody."', '"Morning,Job,Awesome"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"People know who I am or are fans of \'Chelsea Lately,\' and that makes my shows more fun. People know I\'m silly and are on board with what I\'m bringing to the table. I see the boyfriends who got dragged to the show by their girlfriends, and by the end, they\'re laughing harder than anybody. That\'s the best feeling: \'I knew I was going to get you.\'"', '"Best,I Am,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"I worked with the Groundlings, doing sketch comedy and improv at a theater here in L.A. It was my hobby, but I took classes and stayed passionate about it because it\'s what I wanted to do. It just fit. It takes a while before you can actually make money at it. I worked for years."', '"Money,Comedy,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"I do comedy at a lot of colleges, and at the end of those shows, I take time to be a little more real with audiences. I try to inspire them to follow their dreams. When I was that age, it was incredible to hear stuff like that."', '"Dreams,Time,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"I\'m from a small town in North Carolina and went to a small college and didn\'t think that someone like me could make a living in L.A. doing comedy. I worked hard, especially in college, but at that age, you don\'t know what\'s next."', '"Age,Me,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"I would say my career is in a very good place. I\'m in a place of a lot of hope for what\'s next. I see something great, but I\'m not quite there."', '"Hope,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8a', '"My Southern heritage is a big part of who I am. I grew up around people who seemed like characters but are actual, real people. My grandmother made sure I had manners and all that stuff."', '"I Am,People,Heritage"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"You might not be able to control your circumstances, but you can control your response to your circumstances."', '"Control,Circumstances,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"\'Hannity\' had a a guy on that said, \'I fathered 20 kids by 14 mothers.\' That is s cultural issue which has demeaned our society and has caused our society dearly in terms of imprisonment. Who\'s going to be the fathers to those children? Who\'s going to pay child support?"', '"Society,Support,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"The collusion of big business, big labor, and big government threaten the spirit of small business that makes America great."', '"Business,Great,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"I\'ve said before, the number one thing that we have to work on is protecting the gay community from sharia law. Now, in the United States, it\'s probably not a big issue right now, but my brother-in-law is gay, and his partner and I would like them to be able to travel any place in the world without them risking harm."', '"Work,Travel,Community"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"President Obama\'s over in Indonesia when guys like me were at a paper route. President Obama, I don\'t know what experience he had at that same age when he was in Indonesia. So I think it\'s hard for him to grasp that America entrepreneurial spirit."', '"Experience,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"The press called me a billionaire, and my wife came up and said I must be squirreling money away."', '"Money,Wife,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"What do wealthy people do with their money? They can only buy so many cars, houses, and steak dinners. So we either give it away or invest it."', '"Money,People,Buy"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"I think culture precedes politics, and I think the attempts to try and legislate people\'s behavior... isn\'t going to be productive until the culture decides what they want to achieve."', '"Politics,Culture,Behavior"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
