	('394366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', 'I am absolutely stunned how the Democrats were able to somehow say that the Republicans had a war on women... What was the war on women?', '"War,Women,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"There\'s a group of people - maybe the secular Taliban is a good name for them - who have morphed this idea, that you have to accept my values being every bit as cherished as your values. That\'s not tolerance... There are too many things in this world which we sit back and tolerate."', '"Good,World,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
