	('394376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"It can be tough to find areas where Left and Right can agree. Consider the well-being of children: Americans often disagree about how to raise kids, how to educate them, even what to feed them."', '"Children,Well-Being,Tough"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
