	('394379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8b', '"The United Nations Children\'s Fund reports that more than 18 million children worldwide have lost both parents to the ravages of AIDS, starvation, war or natural disasters."', '"War,Lost,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
