	('394383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', '"My family never missed a visit in eight months, ever. I cried coming out. I didn\'t cry coming in. There\'s a big difference. I believe that God put me there for a reason, Incarceration is serious."', '"Family,God,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
