	('394385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', '"I\'ve never stabbed, hurt, killed, stolen, anything, but I went to jail for a year. What is that? My pastor said to me the fact that I\'m not living under a bridge as a crazy woman, talking to myself, is amazing."', '"Amazing,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
