	('394391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', 'I am racing to the studio the moment that God affords me the opportunity to hear again.', '"God,Moment,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', 'The Foxy character and Inga Marchand are two different people. My fiance calls me Inga. No one around me calls me Foxy. I go to church every Sunday. I go to Bible study every Friday night. I\'m saved.', '"Character,Night,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', '"Put out great music, and that\'s that."', '"Music,Great,Out"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', 'I\'m a child of the Women\'s Movement. I always believed that I could do anything. That women didn\'t have to be limited in any way.', '"Women,Way,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8c', 'I devoted my career to building an affinity with my fans who have supported me unflinchingly and no barbed wire fence or prison wall will stop that.', '"Me,Fans,Prison"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
