	('394418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"Every time you go to the doctor and get a good report, the odds keep staking more in your favour."', '"Time,Good,Doctor"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"I told her I wanted a plastic surgeon to sew me up, and I wanted her to freeze my ovaries, so I could harvest the eggs and have a biological child through a surrogate."', '"Me,Harvest,Surgeon"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'Life is precious and there\'s not a lot of room for anger.', '"Life,Anger,Precious"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'I had my moments when I got very frightened that I would not recover.', '"Moments,Would,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"You know I think that going into therapy is a very positive thing, and talking about it is really helpful, because the more you talk the more your fears fade, because you get it out."', '"Positive,Know,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"Well, every time I get ready to do a job I want to lose weight."', '"Time,Lose,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'I started as a teenager going up on commercials.', '"Up,Going,Started"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'I did a terrible television pilot that was so badly written and dumb that it became a turning point for me and I decided that I would never accept a job just because I needed the money.', '"Money,Me,Dumb"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"I like to cook, walk on the beach, go to concerts and look at fine art."', '"Art,Walk,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'It was a small provincial place with great people and I had a happy childhood growing up in Queens.', '"Great,Childhood,People"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"I like writing better. Because I don\'t have to wear makeup, I don\'t have to be thin, and I don\'t have to remember lines."', '"Remember,Better,Makeup"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'I was popular. I wasn\'t the most popular. But I definitely held my own.', '"My Own,Own,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:48:00', '2023-05-29 11:48:00'),
	('394430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'I choose the places I go to carefully and wisely. I\'ll rarely go to a shopping mall anymore.', '"Shopping,Go,Choose"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"Well, my favorite color I guess I would say yellow."', '"Yellow,Well,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', '"Being famous gets me good concert tickets, good tables in restaurants, good seats at sporting events and that\'s really about it."', '"Good,Famous,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8e', 'Well I could have been just a writer. I had been a hair dresser. I could have stuck with that.', '"Hair,Well,Stuck"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I like to wear the same kind of boots that I\'ve worn in training going up to the game so that I\'ve got a feel for the boots.', '"Game,Training,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Especially in front of my dad, I don\'t like being weak. I don\'t like crying in front of my dad because I don\'t want to make him cry."', '"Dad,Cry,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"When my mum passed away, I was very young, and I became very introverted and very quiet. I became very anxious about what people thought about me."', '"Me,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"When I turned 17, that\'s when it all got a bit too much. I decided to stop doing pretty much everything. I quit football. I wouldn\'t get up in the morning. I wouldn\'t go out of my room. I was very depressed."', '"Morning,Football,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"That\'s one thing I relish, the pressure of having to try and beat the best teams in the world."', '"Best,World,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"For me, I want to be scoring goals. That\'s what I\'m judged on, and that\'s what I judge myself on."', '"Myself,Me,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I joined the international stage quite late. I didn\'t do many of the youth age groups, so to come into the senior team and to be offered a Nike deal - a very, very low Nike deal to start with - but I was jumping up to bite the woman\'s hand off to sign the piece of paper."', '"Age,Youth,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"My mum was massively important to everything I\'ve done, and now her memory is a motivational tool for me."', '"Motivational,Me,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'People expect you to dribble past 10 players and put the ball in the back of the net.', '"Past,People,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I want to make sure I\'m a role model for young girls and play the best I can for my team and my country.', '"Best,Country,Role Model"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"My mum is still present in my life. Every goal I score, I dedicate to her. When I am not doing well, I also think about her."', '"Life,I Am,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Now I have a deal with Swarovski! Growing up, my grandma, mum, and I collected the crystals, so that is really incredible."', '"Growing Up,Now,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I\'m happy to stay at Chelsea as long as they\'re happy to have me.', '"Me,Long,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I just want to keep improving myself as a player and a person and hopefully continue to enjoy being on the pitch.', '"Myself,Person,Continue"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"You see now more girls getting involved in their sports because they can see it on TV and see these people playing, and I think - the more and more it\'s exposed and is out there - it will continue to grow and grow. They watch it on TV and think, \'Well, that could be me!\'"', '"Sports,Me,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I\'ve got massive respect for Marta, I\'ve loved watching her play, and I love seeing what she does on the ball. If I can try and emulate that in any way, then I\'m going to be happy with it."', '"Love,Respect,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Every time I score, I celebrate like the kid I was playing in the park."', '"Time,Celebrate,Park"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"It\'s what every kid dreams of: winning a World Cup for your country. There\'s nothing that will ever, ever beat that or even compare to it."', '"Dreams,World,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Women\'s sport is growing, becoming powerful, and we want to continue to raise that platform for the young girls at home."', '"Women,Home,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'It is great to see kits designed specifically with us in mind.', '"Great,Mind,See"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I really enjoy putting the ball in the back of the net. I enjoy being the person that\'s creating things for the team.', '"Back,Person,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Me and my mum were really close. She\'d come to all my football games; she was the one who was always there. If it was raining, and I didn\'t want to go, she\'d say, \'Get in the car!\'"', '"Car,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I\'m very secretive about my feelings, very shy."', '"Feelings,Shy,About"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"A lot of people recognise me now, especially the younger generations, definitely. But it\'s not that common."', '"Me,People,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"We want to be the face of women\'s football, to encourage young girls to play. If I have to be recognised in the streets to encourage them, I\'m happy to do that."', '"Women,Football,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Ultimately, we need to grow the women\'s game. That\'s the biggest issue; it always has been. Then you can talk about equal pay and everything else."', '"Women,Game,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Ultimately, we are doing the same job as the men, but I understand that we\'re not filling out stadiums."', '"Men,Doing,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I want to pave the path as much as possible for the younger girls coming through.', '"Path,Possible,Coming"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"For me, I want to put football in the best possible way: where the girls play professionally, get the sponsorships they deserve, and set themselves up after football so that they\'re not struggling and asking themselves what they\'re going to do."', '"Best,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"That\'s what all of us want, why we\'re getting involved in so many campaigns - we want to leave football in a better place than when we came into it."', '"Football,Better,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I\'ve come out of myself as a person at Chelsea and expressed myself on and off the pitch.', '"Myself,Person,Chelsea"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I\'ve had so many coaches that have helped me along the way through my journey, who understand me and know me as a person."', '"Journey,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"When people ask me what I think about when I\'m playing, I picture myself as a 10-year-old girl, playing in the park, scoring a goal and then celebrating. That\'s when I\'m playing best."', '"Best,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I want to make my family proud as much as possible.', '"Family,Proud,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I used to have a little Geordie accent when I was younger; they called me Little Geordie Fran.', '"Me,Accent,Younger"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'I was playing at sixth form - training in the morning and going to the gym in the afternoon. I was doing my studying alongside it; then I\'d go to training from eight to 10 at night.', '"Morning,Night,Training"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"A lot of my life has been, \'Fran plays football.\' But no, Fran is a normal human being, and I need to live my life."', '"Life,Football,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Before my mum passed away, I was a very extroverted person; I was very outgoing. I didn\'t care what people thought about me."', '"Me,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I\'ve accepted now that it\'s okay not to be okay. It is okay to be upset, and it is okay to need to talk to someone."', '"Upset,Talk,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"Obviously when I was younger, when I was three years old, I used to kick a football around in the park or in the garden. I\'ve got loads of videos, pictures of me doing it."', '"Football,Me,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"I just remember playing in my school and then getting invited to go along to train with a development squad at Reading. My first training session, the manager said, \'You have to come and play with the academy girls,\' so that would probably be my first footballing memory."', '"Training,Memory,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"It\'s always in our mind-set to encourage young girls to get playing. The only way we can do that is being positive off the pitch, trying to engage as much as possible."', '"Positive,Way,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', '"We\'re trying to win a World Cup for our country, and I think everyone who supports football can get behind that."', '"Football,World,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd8f', 'Everything I do is to make mum proud. I\'m sure I\'ve done that.', '"Done,Proud,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"I wanted to be an actor from a young age, but actually becoming one and seen the ugly side of the world does feel different and sometimes unwelcome. There are shallow, vapid, untalented people zombieing the streets of Hollywood, adding decadence and immorality to an already extravagant business."', '"Business,Age,World"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', 'I\'m not the biggest comic book fan.', '"Comic,Fan,Book"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"Horror is so often a \'thinkless\' genre, sort of considered popcorn movies, but you really put a lot of, not just heart and soul, but a lot of physical energy into it."', '"Movies,Heart,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"It\'s a rare thing when you read a role and have this immediate ownership over it, you have this take and this connection, and it\'s not even that you feel that you\'re gonna do a good job, it\'s that you feel like you\'ve found it. It fits, it\'s natural; it\'s like putting on a good shoe or something."', '"Good,Feel,Connection"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"I mean, horror films in general put humans in these awful supernatural or horrible situations, but \'Cabin In The Woods\' cranks it up a few notches and becomes outrageous and totally bizarre."', '"Woods,Mean,Horrible"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"As a professional actor, I don\'t have much choice about what I\'ve gotten into. I tend to be cast in comedies and I\'m fine with that."', '"Choice,Professional,Fine"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', 'There are actors who aren\'t on the cover of magazines but still decide what work they want and when they want it. I want a family one day. So I dream of really being able to decide when to work and when not to.', '"Work,Family,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"That\'s what I love about acting, is playing different roles. I want to work for the character, and not make it work for me."', '"Love,Work,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"When I was a kid, I would make these incredibly bloody movies in my back yard. I was constantly making weird blood concoctions; Jell-O and milk was a good one. I was constantly ruining clothes and staining my parents\' walls and stuff."', '"Good,Movies,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"I know that I\'ve played a lot of comedic roles. It\'s a visual medium. When you get one role, you start to get cast in that role for awhile because that\'s what people have seen you do, and have hopefully seen you do it successfully."', '"People,Start,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd90', '"The actors I respect are the real character actors, who are the real chameleon actors that completely change from role to role. I love Peter Sellers, Alec Guinness and Gary Oldman. They tend to be British, I guess. People who really disappear and transform, I really like that."', '"Love,Change,Respect"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'You\'re only as good as your last haircut.', '"Funny,Good,Haircut"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'The opposite of talking isn\'t listening. The opposite of talking is waiting.', '"Waiting,Listening,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"Great people talk about ideas, average people talk about things, and small people talk about wine."', '"Great,People,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'Life is something to do when you can\'t get to sleep.', '"Life,Sleep,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'Food is an important part of a balanced diet.', '"Funny,Food,Diet"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'Remember that as a teenager you are in the last stage of your life when you will be happy to hear the phone is for you.', '"Life,Remember,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"In real life, I assure you, there is no such thing as algebra."', '"Life,Real,Real Life"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'There is no such thing as inner peace. There is only nervousness or death. Any attempt to prove otherwise constitutes unacceptable behavior.', '"Death,Peace,Behavior"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'My favorite animal is steak.', '"Food,Animal,Steak"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"Very few people possess true artistic ability. It is therefore both unseemly and unproductive to irritate the situation by making an effort. If you have a burning, restless urge to write or paint, simply eat something sweet and the feeling will pass."', '"Art,Sweet,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"Stand firm in your refusal to remain conscious during algebra. In real life, I assure you, there is no such thing as algebra."', '"Life,Real,Stand"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'I figure you have the same chance of winning the lottery whether you play or not.', '"Chance,Winning,Lottery"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"In the Soviet Union, capitalism triumphed over communism. In this country, capitalism triumphed over democracy."', '"Democracy,Capitalism,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'I\'ve done the calculation and your chances of winning the lottery are identical whether you play or not.', '"Winning,Done,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"When you leave New York, you are astonished at how clean the rest of the world is. Clean is not enough."', '"World,Rest,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"I place a high moral value on the way people behave. I find it repellent to have a lot, and to behave with anything other than courtesy in the old sense of the word - politeness of the heart, a gentleness of the spirit."', '"Heart,Value,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"Romantic love is mental illness. But it\'s a pleasurable one. It\'s a drug. It distorts reality, and that\'s the point of it. It would be impossible to fall in love with someone that you really saw."', '"Love,Romantic,Love Is"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
