	('394535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', '"Do not, on a rainy day, ask your child what he feels like doing, because I assure you that what he feels like doing, you won\'t feel like watching."', '"Day,Feel,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
