	('394542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd91', 'Designer clothes worn by children are like snowsuits worn by adults. Few can carry it off successfully.', '"Children,Clothes,Carry"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"If you wait for the right time or the good times to start a business, you wait all your life."', '"Life,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', 'Ignoring facts does not make them go away.', '"Facts,Go,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"What\'s so wonderful about football and business and show business is that every time I start thinking I\'m special, I get knocked on my ass."', '"Business,Time,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"The pro athlete is a sad tale. He signs a big contract and thinks he\'s set for life. I didn\'t think I was set for life, and I don\'t now. As athletes, we are important, celebrities, in demand and rich. Then we are out of the game and we are not important, not celebrities, not in demand and not rich."', '"Life,Sad,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"You can only learn by opening yourself up to engage with different sources of information. How can you learn something if you never see it, read it, or hear it?"', '"Yourself,Information,See"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"If football taught me anything about business, it is that you win the game one play at a time."', '"Business,Time,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"The New York Times Bestseller \'The Amateur,\' written by Ed Klein, former editor of the \'New York Times Magazine,\' is one of the best books I\'ve read."', '"Best,New,Magazine"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"You know, quarterbacks, I think greatness in quarterbacks is taking what you\'ve got, whether it\'s a great team, a good team, or a struggling team and make them better."', '"Good,Great,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', 'Television isn\'t my career. Business is.', '"Business,Television,Career"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"In sports, teams win and individuals don\'t."', '"Sports,Win,Individuals"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"Quarterbacks need to make their team better. If it\'s a bad team, they can even make a bad team better."', '"Bad,Better,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"Great quarterbacks, good quarterbacks, make plays."', '"Good,Great,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', 'That\'s how I judge a quarterback: Either you make plays or you don\'t. I don\'t even want to talk about mechanics.', '"Talk,Judge,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd92', '"The greatness of America is capitalism, free market capitalism. The exceptionalism of American business."', '"Business,Free,America"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd93', '"I think we go when it\'s time to go, that the departures are scheduled."', '"Time,Go,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd93', '"Me, I\'ve been lucky to be good at happiness."', '"Happiness,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd93', 'I would never dare say that I\'m an artist.', '"Never,Dare,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd93', '"For me, artists are the world\'s pain receptors. That is why they have such a hard time living."', '"Time,Pain,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"To survive and even thrive in a changing world, nature offers another great lesson: the survivors are those who at the least adapt to change, or even better learn to benefit from change and grow intellectually and personally. That means careful listening and constant learning."', '"Nature,Change,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Give up the thought that you have control. You don\'t. The best you can do is adapt, anticipate, be flexible, sense the environment and respond."', '"Best,Control,Adapt"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Science and technology are going to be the basis for many of the solutions to social problems.', '"Science,Technology,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'The code of life is like a Beethoven symphony. We have not yet learned how to write music like that. But evolution does it very well. I am learning how to use evolution to compose new music.', '"Life,Learning,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"The fuel for evolution is diversity, with natural selection leading to continuous adaptations and improvements in Nature\'s handiwork."', '"Nature,Diversity,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'What we need is a strong education system that allows creativity to grow and encourages students to be interested in science and technology.', '"Education,Science,Technology"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I can\'t imagine not being able to read and write, or make these connections from literature and philosophy that have helped inform my understanding of evolution."', '"Understanding,Literature,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Enzymes catalyze all the reactions of life. They\'re what allow you to extract materials and energy from your environment and turn that into muscle and tissue and fat. That\'s all done by enzymes. They\'re pretty remarkable chemists - they\'re even better than Caltech chemists.', '"Life,Energy,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Using the power of protein engineering and evolution, we can convince enzymes to take what they do poorly and do it really well."', '"Power,Protein,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I was the first female cab driver in the city of Pittsburgh.', '"City,First,Driver"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Pittsburgh was a wonderful place to grow up - diverse and complex, one could go from one culture to a completely different one in just a few blocks. It was a whole world in one city."', '"Culture,World,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I was very head-strong, and this was the Vietnam War era - You did not listen to your parents or other authority figures. You didn\'t share their values. No one did in my circle. It was OK to rebel."', '"War,Parents,Circle"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Life is not a piece of cake, and it certainly is not for many of the people I know."', '"Life,Cake,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'There\'s plenty of ordinary Nobel laureates.', '"Ordinary,Nobel,Plenty"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I learned how to navigate the world, and life\'s potholes, in Pittsburgh."', '"Life,World,Navigate"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I care about this beautiful planet that we all share. This is a home that we have to leave in good shape for the next generations.', '"Good,Home,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'The biological world always seems poised to innovate.', '"World,Always,Seems"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I decided that I wanted to become an engineer of the biological world, specifically a protein engineer."', '"World,Protein,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'What I want to do is encourage women to take on this incredibly exciting and fun challenge to use their brains for the benefit of humanity but through science and technology.', '"Science,Women,Technology"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I see a future in which nature gives us a helping hand. Instead of destroying the natural world, why can\'t we use it to solve the kinds of problems that we are facing?"', '"Nature,Future,World"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Enzymes are masters of chemistry. They evolved over billions of years to perform specific biological functions. They make complex materials with virtually no waste.', '"Chemistry,Complex,Waste"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I did all sorts of things that you wouldn\'t normally find on an engineer\'s docket, but it made an educated person out of me."', '"Me,Person,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'We\'ve been tinkering with nature for tens of thousands of years - look at a poodle! So we\'ve created all sorts of organisms and biological things that wouldn\'t be here were it not for us.', '"Nature,Look,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Mother Nature has been the best bioengineer in history. Why not harness the evolutionary process to design proteins?', '"Nature,Best,History"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'You never know what will happen tomorrow.', '"Tomorrow,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I don\'t sit around feeling sorry for myself. There\'s always somebody who\'s a lot worse off than you.', '"Myself,Always,Sit"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'People are really interested in these fundamental questions: Why is life based on carbon and not silicon?', '"Life,People,Questions"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I am a student of evolution and adaptation.', '"I Am,Evolution,Student"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I get these students who come in and say, I want to help people. I say, people get plenty of help. Why don\'t you help the planet?"', '"People,Help,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"All my projects are about sustainability, bioremediation, making things in a cleaner fashion."', '"Sustainability,Fashion,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Human beings have been manipulating the biological world for thousands of years without understanding how DNA codes function.', '"World,Understanding,DNA"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"We share deep admiration for evolution, a force of Nature that has led to the finest chemistry of all time, and to all living things on this planet."', '"Nature,Time,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I tried lots of things and never stopped learning.', '"Learning,Never,Tried"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"In academics, it\'s getting your voice out that\'s important. It\'s getting somebody to listen to you. I had no problem with that. People were always curious about what I had to say."', '"People,Important,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Silicon is all around but it\'s tied up in rocks... with these very strong silicon-oxygen bonds that living systems would have to break in order to use silicon.', '"Rocks,Living,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I\'ve done that my whole life - I\'ve taken the way people think and turned it on its head.', '"Life,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"In the lab, we\'re discovering that nature can do chemistry we never dreamed was possible."', '"Nature,Never,Chemistry"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"My feeling is that if a human being can coax life to build bonds between silicon and carbon, nature can do it too."', '"Life,Nature,Build"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"We are going to see a steady stream, I predict, of Nobel prizes coming out of chemistry and given to women."', '"Women,See,Chemistry"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I\'m not a gentleman and I\'m not a scientist.', '"Gentleman,Scientist"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I realized that the way most people were going about protein engineering was doomed failure.', '"Failure,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Nature is solving all sorts of problems that we throw at her - how to degrade plastic bottles, how to degrade pesticides and herbicides and antibiotics. She creates new enzymes in response to that all the time, in real time."', '"Nature,Time,Problems"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Someone asked me \'What\'s the funniest thing or what\'s the best thing that you\'ve ever done?\' It\'s always what I\'m doing now.', '"Best,Me,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I think of what I do as copying nature\'s design process.', '"Nature,Design,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'So many things in my life have gone awry.', '"Life,My Life,Gone"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"There are lot of brilliant women in chemistry, a little later than some of the men, but they are amazing."', '"Women,Men,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I\'ve been called pushy and aggressive and all the negative words that are rarely applied to men with the same traits. But it doesn\'t bother me.', '"Men,Me,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I get called lots of things - a biochemist, a molecular biologist, a chemical engineer - and I guess I am all of those. I identify most as human!"', '"I Am,Human,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"No human can design a good enzyme, yet we are surrounded by them after 3.5 billion years of work by evolution."', '"Work,Good,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Instead of studying what biology has already made, we have to imagine what biology could make. You can say, \'Oh, I want a cure for cancer,\' but that doesn\'t tell you what evolutionary pathway will take you from here to there. What are the intermediate steps?"', '"Biology,Will,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I wanted to develop a career where I could use my engineering background to have a positive effect on society.', '"Positive,Society,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I had to grow up, reach a certain age where I see people do have something to show me."', '"Age,Me,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I do something to make things nature never made but which is useful to humans.', '"Nature,Never,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Only by ignorance is science threatened.', '"Science,Ignorance,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Nature\'s made much more dangerous things than I ever will.', '"Nature,Will,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'When I started engineering proteins I didn\'t know how hard it would be.', '"Know,Engineering,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I thought to myself: What are the most important problems that society faces that I could contribute to? And it was clear that finding new sustainable sources of energy was the most important.', '"Society,Myself,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I meet so many young people who want to plan out their lives and want a recipe. They want me to tell them how to succeed. I didn\'t follow a recipe. I followed my instincts.', '"Me,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I was lucky to be passionate about a field that was full of opportunity.', '"Opportunity,Field,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Most innovative things are not obvious to other people at the time. You have to believe in yourself. If you\'ve got a good idea, follow it even though others tell you it\'s not."', '"Time,Good,Believe In Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Doing science at the highest level is hard for anyone. It\'s hard for women, and it\'s hard for the men. And we need to have supportive mentors and role models we can look up to."', '"Science,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"For me, I was always the only woman in my cohort, first as a mechanical engineering undergraduate student, then as a chemical engineering graduate student. There were very few women getting degrees in those fields at the time. My role models were men - great men role models."', '"Women,Time,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'What I want to do is demonstrate that biology can learn how to make a vast array of molecules that people thought were outside the realm of biology.', '"People,Biology,Outside"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'My feeling is that we can genetically encode almost any kind of chemistry. We just have to learn how to do that.', '"Chemistry,Feeling,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I was employed at the Solar Energy Research Institute in the late \'70s when Carter was president, and as a country, we had a goal of renewable energy development."', '"Energy,Research,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Engineering the biological world was even more interesting than engineering the mechanical world.', '"World,Engineering,More"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I wanted to make enzymes that would solve human problems, not just problems for a cell that makes them."', '"Problems,Human,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Microbes such as bacteria and yeast use enzymes to make fuels from biomass. We use directed evolution to perfect those enzymes and make new fuels efficiently.', '"Perfect,New,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Evolution is good for optimising and that is well understood. But evolution also creates things that no one knew were even possible.', '"Good,Possible,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"In the test tube, I can make any DNA I want, recombining it from monkeys, worms, anywhere. So I can explore new rules of breeding with molecules."', '"New,Rules,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I studied mechanical engineering at Princeton and worked on solar energy after graduation.', '"Graduation,Energy,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I took mechanical drawing, geometry and typing at high school, the latter because that is what they did with smart girls in those days!"', '"Smart,Drawing,School"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I\'m an engineer by training.', '"Training,Engineer"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Proteins aren\'t designed, they\'re evolved."', '"Proteins,Designed,Evolved"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I wanted to rewrite the code of life, to make new molecular machines that would solve human problems."', '"Life,Problems,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Bemoaning your fate is not going to solve the problem.', '"Fate,Your,Problem"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I love what I do, and I\'m grateful for every day I can do it."', '"Love,Day,Grateful"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I know how to do science. I know how to make things. I don\'t know how to run a company. Now that\'s a really tough job.', '"Science,Tough,Company"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"I\'m interested in using evolution to move forward into the future, to get biology to do a lot of new chemistry for us."', '"Future,New,Biology"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I feel a responsibility to encourage everyone to excel in science.', '"Science,Responsibility,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"We all need friends, and friends are there to hold you up when nothing else can."', '"Nothing,Need,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Isobutanol is not a natural product, but we evolved an enzyme that makes it possible to convert plant sugars to this precursor to jet fuel."', '"Plant,Product,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Evolution, to me, is the best designer of all time."', '"Best,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I was used to being the only woman in everything... I didn\'t even think about it. Men were my role models - there\'s nothing wrong with that.', '"Men,Woman,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"For some reason, there are political forces that somehow feel threatened by honest inquiry. How can you be threatened by wanting to know the facts?"', '"Political,Facts,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Only engineers would do something like random mutagenesis.', '"Random,Only,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'Cellulose has physical and chemical properties that make it difficult to access and difficult to break down.', '"Difficult,Down,Break"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'The DNA-encoded catalytic machinery of the cell can rapidly learn to promote new chemical reactions when we provide new reagents and the appropriate incentive in the form of artificial selection.', '"New,Incentive,Chemical"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"This innovation machine that\'s evolution, we can use it to do all sorts of interesting things."', '"Innovation,Evolution,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'We\'ve been modifying the biological world at the level of DNA for thousands of years. Somehow there is this new fear of what we already have been doing and that fear has limited our ability to provide real solutions.', '"Fear,World,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'I\'d like to see what fraction of things that chemists have figured out we could actually teach nature to do. Then we really could replace chemical factories with bacteria.', '"Nature,See,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'What I find most interesting is what nature can do if you only ask.', '"Nature,Find,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'The real frontier is making these hybrid systems where you expand the capabilities of biology with chemistry.', '"Biology,Real,Chemistry"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Inside of a living cell there are thousands of proteins that enable it to make more of itself and make your malaria drug, for instance. We don\'t understand those. We don\'t understand how they work together."', '"Work,Together,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'We\'re seeing a move toward making things that either chemistry cannot make or can\'t make efficiently but biology does.', '"Biology,Chemistry,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', 'There\'s nothing like evolution for engineering beautiful organisms.', '"Beautiful,Nothing,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"My whole interest is, how do you use evolution as an innovation engine? How does evolution solve new problems that life faces? And to have a system that can create a whole new chemical bond that biology hasn\'t done before, to me, demonstrates the power of nature to innovate."', '"Life,Nature,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"Silicon-based life on Earth doesn\'t make sense, but perhaps it would in some totally different environment."', '"Life,Earth,Environment"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"In the universe of possibilities that exist for life, we\'ve shown that it is a very easy possibility for life as we know it to include silicon in organic molecules. And once you can do it somewhere in the universe, it\'s probably being done."', '"Life,You Can Do It,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd94', '"My laboratory uses evolution to design new enzymes. No one really knows how to design them - they are tremendously complicated. But we are learning how to use evolution to make new ones, just as nature does."', '"Nature,Learning,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd95', 'I can swear like a fishwife.', '"I Can,Like,Swear"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd95', '"I always wanted to be an actress. And it wasn\'t ego. I felt so little about myself, considered myself such a sparrow. Not just my size. I thought I was so plain... I did plays not to show off but because if I did that - I didn\'t realize it at the time - I would be somebody other than this person I didn\'t really approve of."', '"Time,Myself,Ego"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I\'m very lucky because my eyes work with almost any hair color. Thanks for the genetics, parents."', '"Work,Eyes,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I\'ve always felt more comfortable in fantasy. Fantasy has felt more real to me at times. Drawing was an immediate outlet for that: to create. It\'s been my ability to create my own world.', '"Me,World,Drawing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I can count on one hand how many people I trust.', '"Trust,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'How we treat our bodies directly correlates to how we treat our souls. It\'s all interconnected. It has to be.', '"Treat,Interconnected,How"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I find it interesting where grunge originated from and then where it was taken, which was high fashion. My dad was so poor that they kept going to Goodwill to get donated ripped jeans. It wasn\'t a fashion decision; it was an \'I don\'t have any money, I have no other choice\' type of decision."', '"Money,Dad,Decision"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I\'m famous by default. I came out of the womb, and people wanted to know who I was because of my parents."', '"Famous,Parents,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I\'m in a monogamous relationship and very happy.', '"Relationship,Happy,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'The shelf life of an artist or musician isn\'t particularly long.', '"Life,Long,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I am constantly evolving. The moment I stop my evolution is the moment I disservice myself and, ultimately, those I love."', '"Love,Myself,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"Thankfully, I have other skills than just standing there and looking cute."', '"Cute,Looking,Standing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"New York is, like, my dream city."', '"City,New,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I really enjoy the aesthetic of building my fashion sense. I enjoy the process of going through fashion phases.', '"Process,Building,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I don\'t like to look sloppy. I\'m a girly-girl.', '"Look,Like,Sloppy"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I have 137 pairs of shoes and 200 pairs of jeans.', '"Shoes,Jeans,Pairs"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I\'m a different person. I don\'t want to be titled as Courtney Love and Kurt Cobain\'s daughter. I want to be thought of as Frances Cobain.', '"Love,Person,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'My look is a Modern Bohemian type thing.', '"Look,Bohemian,Modern"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"While I\'m generally silent on the affairs of my biological mother, her recent tirade has taken a gross turn."', '"Mother,Turn,Silent"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'Twitter should ban my mother.', '"Mother,Twitter,Ban"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"We\'ve moved so much, and my life has been so inconsistent."', '"Life,My Life,Much"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I\'m really lucky, because I\'ve been able to go places and meet people you can only dream of."', '"People,Go,Meet"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'It\'s creepy to see fan sites about me.', '"Me,See,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"So I have been careful about where I go and who I hang out with because if you tell someone the wrong thing, then it\'s everywhere."', '"Someone,Wrong,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"These people are fascinated by me, but I haven\'t done anything."', '"Me,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"If you\'re a big Nirvana fan, a big Hole fan, then I understand why you would want to get to know me, but I\'m not my parents."', '"Me,Parents,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"The fact that I\'m sober isn\'t really public knowledge, decidedly and deliberately."', '"Knowledge,Sober,Public"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"As cheesy and cornball as it sounds, life does get better - if you want it to."', '"Life,Better,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"With regards to music, I don\'t want to pigeonhole myself and say I am a musician or a visual artist, because I feel like it\'s all-encompassing, and I feel like every bit of my art is related to the other."', '"Art,Music,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I don\'t really like Nirvana that much.', '"Like,Much,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'The hardest part of doing anything creatively is just getting up and doing.', '"Doing,Anything,Hardest"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'The grunge scene is not what I\'m interested in.', '"Scene,Grunge,Interested"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"People don\'t follow me around, and they don\'t stop me in a way where it\'s excessive or invasive. It\'s always respectful. If it\'s not, I set my boundaries, and I walk away. That\'s just what you kind of have to do."', '"Walk,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I had a lot of strong women around my whole life who were survivors. My grandma survived breast cancer twice and the death of her child and the death of her brother, and, you know, just a lot of tragedy, and she\'s still the happiest person I\'ve ever met."', '"Life,Death,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'Most of my artwork is geared towards being humorous in some light.', '"Light,Being,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I\'m really outgoing, but there\'s times I want to be by myself."', '"Myself,Want,Outgoing"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', 'I want to be able to live in a way that isn\'t too hectic. Calm. And I want those around me to be sublimely happy as well.', '"Me,Calm,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd96', '"I don\'t model unless I think the project is cool, and I don\'t put my name behind something that I don\'t genuinely believe in."', '"Cool,Believe,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Pollution from human activities is changing the Earth\'s climate. We see the damage that a disrupted climate can do: on our coasts, our farms, forests, mountains, and cities. Those impacts will grow more severe unless we start reducing global warming pollution now."', '"Grow,Start,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Wind and other clean, renewable energy will help end our reliance on fossil fuels and combat the severe threat that climate change poses to humans and wildlife alike."', '"Change,Energy,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Mangroves, salt marshes and sea grass lock away carbon at up to five times the rate of tropical forests."', '"Sea,Grass,Salt"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"California\'s drought affects everyone in the state, from farmers to fishermen, business owners to suburban residents, and everyone has a role to play in using precious water resources as wisely and efficiently as possible."', '"Business,Water,Precious"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"In the end, the market will decide which is the better performer: dirty coal-fired power or clean wind and solar. Market-based competition. That doesn\'t sound like communism to me."', '"Power,Me,Competition"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"I have long understood that climate change is not only an environmental issue - it is a humanitarian, economic, health, and justice issue as well."', '"Change,Health,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"We\'ll always need energy. We need to communicate, too, but we\'re not stuck with hand gestures and smoke signals. There are better ways to power our future than by digging fossil fuel from the ground and setting it on fire."', '"Future,Power,Fire"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Nearly every president in the past 100 years has declared national monuments, from Teddy Roosevelt creating the Grand Canyon National Monument to George W. Bush preserving 10 islands and 140,000 square miles of ocean waters in the Northwestern Hawaiian Islands."', '"Past,Monuments,Ocean"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Tar sands oil is the dirtiest fuel on Earth. Because producing it consumes so much energy, a gallon of tar sands crude generates 17 percent more carbon pollution than conventional crude oil."', '"Energy,Earth,Pollution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"From reinforcing beaches in the Rockaways to installing generators at the Coney Island Houses and sealing holes in the subway system, New York is fortifying our ability to withstand future storm surges."', '"Future,Storm,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"At the start of my career, I fought to prevent offshore drilling along the Atlantic Coast."', '"Start,Drilling,Offshore"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"We must not sacrifice one of our remaining untamed places in reckless pursuit of oil. We know we have to leave oil in the ground, or destructive climate change will become unstoppable. If not in the pristine and vulnerable Arctic Ocean, then where?"', '"Change,Sacrifice,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Under pressure from a growing movement of people who want their money out of fossil fuels, universities, pension investors and foundations are looking to exclude coal, oil and gas stocks from their portfolios."', '"Money,Looking,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'I have talked to people across the country struggling in the face of an altered climate. New Jersey homeowners are trying to rebuild after Superstorm Sandy. Miami government officials are trying to plan for rising seas and flooded streets. California farmers are trying to make it through the state\'s worst drought on record.', '"Government,Face,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Opening up Atlantic and Arctic waters to drilling would lock the next generation into burning oil and gas in a way that only makes climate change that much worse, fueling ever rising seas, widening deserts, withering drought, blistering heat, raging storms, wildfires, floods and other hallmarks of climate chaos."', '"Change,Chaos,Heat"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The phrase \'mad as a hatter\' was coined because hat makers were poisoned by the high levels of mercury used in felt processing; these workers developed a strange, uneven gait as well as strange alterations in their personalities - traits that resembled mental instability."', '"Hat,Mad,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The signs of climate change are visible across the nation, from the drought-stricken fields of Central California to the flooded streets of Michigan. Extreme weather is turning people\'s lives upside down and costing communities millions of dollars in damaged infrastructure and added health care costs."', '"Change,Health,Weather"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Striking a balance between wildlife conservation and wind energy development starts with understanding threats to eagle populations and how our actions, including operating wind farms, are affecting them."', '"Energy,Wind,Balance"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Pollution from oil and gas development, toxic runoff, and miles and miles of plastic trash foul the waters and threaten marine life."', '"Life,Development,Pollution"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Though every nation must do its part to address climate change, developed nations are responsible for the lion\'s share of carbon pollution in the atmosphere, and they have an obligation to help developing nations transition to a sustainable future."', '"Change,Future,Lion"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"When I left school, I never wondered whether my apartment in New York was vulnerable to storm surges, but my three daughters have to consider the realities of extreme weather and how it may destabilize communities around the globe."', '"Weather,Storm,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Shell has poured billions of dollars into offshore Arctic drilling, but no matter how much it spends, it cannot make the effort anything but a terrifying gamble. And if Shell, the most profitable company on Earth, can\'t buy its way to safety in Alaska, nobody can."', '"Effort,Way,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Mercury is a potent toxin that interferes with the human nervous system. Reducing this hazard will be a major public health breakthrough.', '"Health,Will,Nervous"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"I have been fighting climate change for two decades, and people often ask me how I remain hopeful in the face of extreme weather and grim forecasts. The answer is simple: I see countless solutions spreading across the nation and across the world. But we need more investment."', '"Change,Weather,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The Pacific Remote Islands Marine National Monument may be distant from our shores, but it will help us understand how healthy marine ecosystems work and how we can revive troubled seas closer to home."', '"Work,Home,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Once a landscape is industrialized, its wild character is lost for good. You can\'t recreate untouched tundra, mountain meadows, crystal clear streams, and animals that have never encountered toxic waste."', '"Good,Character,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Though many corporations honor commitments to reduce dangerous pollution, some cut corners and cheat. The marketplace doesn\'t always have mechanisms to correct bad actors."', '"Honor,Bad,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'We can power our economy without despoiling our wild places.', '"Power,Wild,Places"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Instead of hazarding our future on the dirty fuels of the past, let\'s invest in clean power that can drive this country forward. Let\'s cut energy waste, make our economy the world\'s most efficient, and give our workers a leg up in the global marketplace."', '"Future,Power,World"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Declaring the San Gabriel Mountains a national monument will make this natural wonder more accessible. It will welcome people from all walks of life and maintain the mountains\' wild character at the same time.', '"Life,Time,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'I do believe that the coal industry sees the cultural shift toward cleaner energy and global warming solutions as a threat to their interests.', '"Believe,Energy,Global Warming"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Green roofs, roadside plantings, porous pavement, and sidewalk gardens have been proven to reduce flooding. They absorb rainwater before it swamps the streets and sewage systems."', '"Green,Streets,Before"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The fossil fuel industry commands outsize sway over U.S. politics, markets, and democracy. I knew these companies were formidable, but when I served on the National Commission on the BP Deepwater Horizon Oil Spill and Offshore Drilling, I got a close up view of how the industry disregards government safeguards."', '"Politics,Government,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Studies show that women are more likely than men to die in natural disasters. Women\'s voices must be heard.', '"Women,Men,Die"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Whether it is salt farmers in India embracing solar power or wind companies creating tens of thousands of jobs in America, people are providing a vision for the clean energy future."', '"Future,Power,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"I attended the climate talks in Copenhagen in 2009, and back then, national governments waited until days before to submit climate plans, and the U.S. based its pledge on a proposed bill that would fail in the Senate."', '"Back,Climate,Pledge"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Countries have made impressive pledges to cut carbon pollution, but we have to ensure these promises become actions."', '"Pollution,Promises,Carbon"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"We look back at the 1990 Clean Air Act amendments, where people screamed and hollered it\'s going to be too expensive, they couldn\'t afford it, and it wouldn\'t work. And it worked. It worked faster than people expected, at much less cost."', '"Work,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Putting a tax on carbon could be an effective approach for curbing global warming pollution.', '"Global Warming,Pollution,Carbon"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'A cap on carbon is important because it sets a specific goal for reducing carbon emissions 80% by 2050.', '"Important,Cap,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"As heat rises, so does the number of people trying to cool down homes, schools, hospitals and businesses. This isn\'t just about comfort; it\'s a matter of public health."', '"Cool,Health,Heat"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Too often, the air conditioners we use to cool down also contribute to climate change - the very force that\'s fueling extreme heat."', '"Cool,Change,Heat"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Safer chemicals and more energy-efficient technologies can provide cooling without severe climate implications. Shifting to these alternatives could avoid the equivalent of 12 times the current annual carbon pollution of the United States by 2050.', '"Climate,Pollution,Avoid"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Shell Oil\'s decision to pull the plug on drilling for oil in the Chukchi Sea is a major victory for the Arctic.', '"Decision,Victory,Sea"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Many environmental battles are won by delaying a destructive project long enough to change the conversation - to allow new economic, political and social dynamics to emerge."', '"Change,Environmental,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"VW has held a beloved place in American culture. When I graduated from college, many of my friends drove across the country, and most hit the road in a VW van or Bug. Through the years, these cars have represented youth, freedom and quirkiness."', '"Freedom,Youth,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Our nation has abundant clean energy resources, and tapping them will generate jobs, make the air safer to breathe, and tackle climate change - the greatest environmental crisis of our time."', '"Change,Time,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"When climate change supercharges weather patterns, the disadvantaged often suffer first and most."', '"Change,Weather,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Instead of going to the ends of the Earth - and plumbing the depths of the oceans - to squeeze out every last drop of oil, we need, instead, to do everything we can to reduce the risks of offshore oil and gas production."', '"Risks,Earth,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Business leaders, social justice groups, farmers and ranchers, doctors and nurses and people from all walks of life are concerned about the climate threat."', '"Life,Business,Justice"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'I have visited people whose health has been endangered by tar sands oil. I have watched neighbors struggle to recover from Superstorm Sandy. I have seen solar panels and wind turbines become an increasingly familiar part of the landscape.', '"Health,Struggle,Wind"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Climate change deniers would have us believe that oil, gas, and coal are the only ways to power a modern, industrialized society. They are wrong, and the proof is all around us."', '"Change,Power,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Strong limits on carbon pollution will save Americans money, create jobs, improve our health, and help defuse climate change."', '"Change,Health,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'The Keystone XL pipeline is a threat to our nation. It would increase pollution and intensify climate change for generations to come. We must raise our voices and demand our leaders reject this dirty scheme.', '"Change,Dirty,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"New York and Connecticut belong to the Regional Greenhouse Gas Initiative to cut carbon emissions, and New York City has been a leader in energy efficiency."', '"Energy,City,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Healthy forests and wetlands stand sentry against the dangers of climate change, absorbing carbon dioxide from the atmosphere and locking it away in plants, root systems and soil."', '"Change,Stand,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The U.S. can become carbon neutral in our lifetimes. In the process, we will put millions of Americans to work, make our companies more competitive, and shield our communities from extreme weather. And we will honor our obligation to leave the world a better place for future generations."', '"Work,Future,Weather"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Los Angeles County is one of the most park-poor urban areas in the nation, and the San Gabriel Valley - stretching from Pasadena to Pomona - is especially starved for open space."', '"Space,Valley,Nation"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The San Gabriel monument expands our natural heritage, but there is more in need of safeguarding - extraordinary places like Utah\'s Greater Canyonlands."', '"Heritage,Extraordinary,More"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The San Gabriel Mountains rise like a rampart at the edge of the city, safeguarding more than 500,000 acres of mature forests, mountain streams, dramatic waterfalls, and towering peaks that reach over 9,000 feet. These untamed places attract bighorn sheep, mountain lions, and other threatened or endangered species."', '"City,Feet,Sheep"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The San Gabriel Valley, stretching from Pasadena to Pomona, is especially starved for open space. The valley has a rich array of ethnically diverse communities, but it also has some of the highest rates of childhood obesity and diabetes in the state."', '"Space,Childhood,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'NRDC has helped bring hope spots to more of our shared ocean waters. We helped draft and pass a California law creating a network of underwater parks stretching from the Oregon border to the Mexican border.', '"Hope,Law,Underwater"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The oceans produce up to 70 percent of our oxygen, they shape our climate, and they support an American oceans economy larger than our nation\'s entire agriculture sector."', '"Support,Agriculture,American"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Back when the EPA proposed phasing out ozone-depleting CFCs, the chemical industry howled that refrigerators would fail in America\'s supermarkets, hospitals and schools."', '"America,Back,Industry"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Getting toxic lead out of gasoline, the oil industry shouted, would cost a dollar a gallon. It turned out to cost just a penny a gallon to protect hundreds of thousands of kids from lead-induced brain damage."', '"Brain,Oil,Lead"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Americans welcome carbon limits because they want to protect their families from harm.', '"Welcome,Limits,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The U.S. limits mercury, arsenic, and soot from power plants. Yet, astonishingly, there are no national limits on how much carbon pollution these plants can dump into our atmosphere."', '"Power,Limits,Plants"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The U.S. has a proud history of cleaning up our air through technological innovation. We did it with leaded gas, acid rain and countless other pollutants, and we can do it with carbon pollution, too."', '"History,Rain,Innovation"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Young people are already leading on climate action. I see it at rallies to reject the Keystone XL dirty tar sands pipeline. I see it in the push to demand justice for communities being run over by fracking operations.', '"Justice,Action,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Americans are worried about pollution - oil trains running through their towns, fracking in their neighborhoods, coal dust in their air. They\'re worried about what the future will look like for their children if carbon pollution continues unchecked."', '"Future,Look,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"For decades, NRDC has created and supported policies that will ultimately end our reliance on fossil fuels."', '"Will,End,Fossil Fuels"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"A stock market index helps investors track the performance of a group of stocks. NRDC worked with FTSE to develop comprehensive and transparent methodologies that screen out companies linked to owning, exploring, or extracting fossil fuels."', '"Performance,Stock Market,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"I was in college when tens of thousands of people marched on Washington for the first Earth Day. Raw sewage floated in rivers and clouds of smog hung over cities. But then something amazing happened. People spoke out. Thousands of students, workers, and ordinary citizens used their voices to say, \'This has to change.\'"', '"Change,Amazing,Clouds"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Water efficiency, recycling, and other local supplies will help California flourish in a drier future."', '"Future,Water,Efficiency"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'The truth is you can\'t get more water from reservoirs that are empty.', '"Truth,Water,Empty"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The more people learn about the proposed Keystone XL tar sands pipeline, the worse it looks."', '"People,More,Worse"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"All Americans have benefited from the dedicated service of Representative Henry Waxman. In every battle and in every moment that mattered most, Rep. Waxman stood up for the air we breathe, the water we drink, and the wild places we cherish."', '"Moment,Water,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"After being nearly eradicated from the lower 48 states by the 1960s, bald eagles were re-introduced to the Adirondacks in the 1980s, and I\'m proud to report the view from my home indicates they are flourishing in upstate New York."', '"Home,View,New"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'Protecting eagles from the threat of extinction is a conservation success story that we must prudently safeguard for future generations to come.', '"Success,Future,Story"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Climate change is the central environmental ill of our time. We have an obligation to protect our children from the dangers of this widening scourge, and we aren\'t yet doing enough about it."', '"Change,Time,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The science tells us that if we fail to reduce global warming pollution, global temperatures will rise to dangerous levels and unleash devastating extreme weather events and accelerate destructive sea level rise."', '"Science,Weather,Sea"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'The single most important thing we can do to protect our communities from climate change is to reduce dangerous carbon pollution.', '"Change,Important,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"When the government undertakes or approves a major project such as a dam or highway project, it must make sure the project\'s impacts, environmental and otherwise, are considered. In many cases, NEPA gives the public its only opportunity to be heard about the project\'s impact on their community."', '"Environmental,Government,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'NEPA\'s common sense approach to foster discussion and collaboration about major development projects has worked well to protect our national treasures and resources.', '"Development,Common Sense,Collaboration"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Every year, tens of millions of salmon return to the pristine shores of Bristol Bay in Alaska. They linger in the bay\'s cool, shallow waters before charging up nearby streams to spawn and create another generation of wild salmon."', '"Cool,Generation,Wild"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Mercury is most commonly recognized as a developmental toxin, threatening to young children and fetuses as they develop their nervous system. Prenatal exposure to even low levels of mercury can cause life-long problems with language skills, fine motor function, and the ability to pay attention."', '"Problems,Children,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"In grownups, mercury can cause memory loss, tremors, vision loss and numbness of the fingers and toes. It can also adversely affect fertility and blood pressure regulation, and a growing body of evidence suggests that exposure to mercury may lead to heart disease."', '"Heart,Vision,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Carbon pollution contributes to climate change, which causes temperatures to rise. Hotter temperatures mean more smog in the air, and breathing smog can inflame deep lung tissue. Repeated inflammation over time can permanently scar lung tissue, even in low concentrations."', '"Change,Time,Rise"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Americans are already paying the price for record heat waves, dirty air, and an unstable climate. We need to fight these threats with every weapon we have, and the electricity industry has to do its fair share."', '"Fight,Heat,Dirty"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"When people who love the ocean come together, they can achieve extraordinary things."', '"Love,Together,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"The oceans have been a part of my life for as long as I remember. As a child, I spent hours playing in the surf off Cape Cod. In college, I fished along the rocky coast of Nova Scotia with my school\'s fishing team."', '"Life,Fishing,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"Over the years, I have seen the power of the oceans to excite, feed, and sustain people. I have also seen them undergo a growing onslaught of attacks, from destructive fishing practices to rising acidification."', '"Power,Fishing,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', '"When we go to the store, we bring home more than food - we bring home traces of broader environmental problems. But we can use our shopping carts and dinner plates to help solve some of those problems."', '"Home,Food,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'We can choose food that doesn\'t lead to illnesses like diabetes and cancer. We can choose food that doesn\'t contribute to water pollution and climate change. And we can choose food that keeps local economies vibrant and farmers on their land.', '"Change,Food,Water"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd97', 'The people who harvest America\'s food must be treated with respect and earn a living wage.', '"Respect,Food,Harvest"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', 'Traveling is the ruin of all happiness! There\'s no looking at a building after seeing Italy.', '"Happiness,Travel,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"To whom, then, must I dedicate my wonderful, surprising and interesting adventures? to whom dare I reveal my private opinion of my nearest relations? the secret thoughts of my dearest friends? my own hopes, fears, reflections and dislikes? Nobody!"', '"Thoughts,Opinion,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"A youthful mind is seldom totally free from ambition; to curb that, is the first step to contentment, since to diminish expectation is to increase enjoyment."', '"Mind,Step,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"The mind is but too naturally prone to pleasure, but too easily yielded to dissipation."', '"Mind,Pleasure,Naturally"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', 'I am ashamed of confessing that I have nothing to confess.', '"I Am,Nothing,Ashamed"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"There is something in age that ever, even in its own despite, must be venerable, must create respect and to have it ill treated, is to me worse, more cruel and wicked than anything on earth."', '"Respect,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"I cannot be much pleased without an appearance of truth; at least of possibility I wish the history to be natural though the sentiments are refined; and the characters to be probable, though their behaviour is excelling."', '"Truth,History,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"For my part, I confess I seldom listen to the players: one has so much to do, in looking about and finding out one\'s acquaintance, that, really, one has no time to mind the stage. One merely comes to meet one\'s friends, and show that one\'s alive."', '"Time,Mind,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"To despise riches, may, indeed, be philosophic, but to dispense them worthily, must surely be more beneficial to mankind."', '"Indeed,More,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', 'I cannot sleep - great joy is as restless as great sorrow.', '"Great,Joy,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"But if the young are never tired of erring in conduct, neither are the older in erring of judgment."', '"Tired,Never,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', 'In the bosom of her respectable family resided Camilla.', '"Family,Her,Bosom"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"People who live together naturally catch the looks and air of one another and without having one feature alike, they contract a something in the whole countenance which strikes one as a resemblance."', '"Together,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"Insensibility, of all kinds, and on all occasions, most moves my imperial displeasure."', '"Most,Moves,Kinds"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd98', '"We continually say things to support an opinion, which we have given, that in reality we don\'t above half mean."', '"Reality,Support,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"I guess you\'re happy if you have some kind of balance in you. I\'m a human being. I have days when I feel paralyzed, days when I feel like a slug. Then I have days when I have good energy, I\'ve read the newspaper and I\'ve done different things."', '"Good,Energy,Balance"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"It\'s actually meditative to sit in a character for an extended period of time, realizing what your relationship is to who you\'re playing and then letting go, just being there."', '"Time,Relationship,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"If you choose to be Frankenstein with Botox and plastic surgery, you\'ve bought your own private mask."', '"Mask,Own,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', 'Marriage is an exercise in torture.', '"Marriage,Exercise,Torture"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"\'Six Feet Under\' was so much about life. Sure, it had a lot to do with death, but that\'s the fun - that now I became a dead person."', '"Life,Death,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"As you age naturally, your family shows more and more on your face. If you deny that, you deny your heritage."', '"Family,Age,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', 'I can\'t form a total picture of things. Because I\'m not her.', '"Picture,Because,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"It\'s like real life: We don\'t get a preview of what\'s coming up, thank God, and we don\'t build our own character from what we\'re going to be informed with in the future."', '"Life,God,Future"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"Some people ask me, Do they put aging makeup on you? It\'s just this very nice street makeup."', '"Me,Street,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd99', '"I think the rigors of a TV schedule are brutal and \'Six Feet Under\' wasn\'t a network schedule. We did 13 shows, we didn\'t do 22. I don\'t know how people do that. I really don\'t. I mean the shows are shorter, but wow, it\'s quite a discipline."', '"Discipline,Feet,People"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9a', '"The world is wide, and I will not waste my life in friction when it could be turned into momentum."', '"Life,World,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9a', 'Temperance is moderation in the things that are good and total abstinence from the things that are foul.', '"Good,Things,Moderation"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9a', '"This seems to be the law of progress in everything we do; it moves along a spiral rather than a perpendicular; we seem to be actually going out of the way, and yet it turns out that we were really moving upward all the time."', '"Time,Progress,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9a', '"In externals we advance with lightening express speed, in modes of thought and sympathy we lumber on in stage-coach fashion."', '"Sympathy,Fashion,Speed"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', 'There comes a point when a dream becomes reality and reality becomes a dream.', '"Reality,Point,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I used to lie between cool, clean sheets at night after I\'d had a bath, after I had washed my hair and scrubbed my knuckles and finger-nails and teeth. Then I could lie quite still in the dark with my face to the window with the trees in it, and talk to God."', '"Cool,God,Night"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"If a person is treated like a patient, they are apt to act like one."', '"Medical,Person,Act"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I couldn\'t get that same feeling during the day, with my hands in dirty dish water and the hard sun showing up the dirtiness on the roof tops. And after a time, even at night, the feeling of God didn\'t last."', '"God,Time,Water"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"The Sunday School teacher talked too much in the way our grade school teacher used to when she told us about George Washington. Pleasant, pretty stories, but not true."', '"Teacher,True,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"It puzzled me that other people hadn\'t found out, too. God was gone. We were younger. We had reached past him. Why couldn\'t they see it? It still puzzles me."', '"God,Me,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I just knew that God wasn\'t there. He was a man on a throne in Heaven, so he was easy to forget."', '"God,Man,Heaven"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"But I was sure of one thing. If God were a father, with children, that cleanliness I had been feeling wasn\'t God."', '"God,Father,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I have learned that to have a good friend is the purest of all God\'s gifts, for it is a love that has no exchange of payment."', '"Love,God,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:49:00', '2023-05-29 11:49:00'),
	('394832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I didn\'t think then, and I still don\'t, that I was actually sick."', '"Sick,Think,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I think God just died of old age. And, when I realized that he wasn\'t any more, it didn\'t shock me. It seemed natural and right!"', '"God,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', 'I went to Sunday School and liked the stories about Christ and the Christmas star. They were beautiful. They made you warm and happy to think about. But I didn\'t believe them.', '"Christmas,Beautiful,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"I wondered a little why God was such a useless thing. It seemed a waste of time to have him. After that he became less and less, until he was... nothingness."', '"God,Time,Useless"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"That satisfied me until I began to figure that if God loved all his children equally, why did he bother about my red hat and let other people lose their fathers and mothers for always?"', '"God,Me,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9b', '"The more people pointed at me in scorn the more stubborn I got and when they began calling me the Bad Girl of West Seattle High, I tried to live up to it."', '"Me,Bad,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9c', 'I was not meant to go deer hunting every fall.', '"Fall,Go,Deer"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9c', '"I came from the theater playing leading roles, and when I started doing film and television, I felt as if I had to start from the bottom."', '"Start,Doing,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9c', 'How wonderful it was to sit on a set with Norman Mailer and get to know him.', '"Know,Sit,Wonderful"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Practice self-awareness, self-evaluation, and self-improvement. If we are aware that our manners - language, behavior, and actions - are measured against our values and principles, we are able to more easily embody the philosophy, leadership is a matter of how to be, not how to do."', '"Leadership,Behavior,Practice"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Carry a big basket. In other words, be open to new ideas, different partners, and new practices, and have a willingness to dump out the old and irrelevant to make room for new approaches."', '"Words,New,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"We do not know what lies ahead, yet whatever the challenge, leaders will rise, finding the heart, the language, the caring that embraces and sustains."', '"Heart,Caring,Rise"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Leadership is not a basket of tricks or strategies or skills that you pull out. Leadership begins with the quality of the person.', '"Leadership,Quality,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Planning defines the particular place you want to be and how you intend to get there. It\'s a responsibility rather than a technique.', '"Responsibility,Place,Planning"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Listening is an art.', '"Art,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Leadership is a matter of how to be - not how to do it.', '"Leadership,Matter,How"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Social-sector organizations have to be better managed than for-profit organizations... because they have no margin of error.', '"Better,Because,Error"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"When you see a roadblock or challenge as an opportunity, it is amazing how you are already halfway there."', '"Amazing,Opportunity,See"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"An exceptional career is one that provides an opportunity to serve. It is a satisfying career in which you can\'t wait to get up in the morning to begin! You have a sense of purpose and mission. You know why you do what you do. It is a response to a call to serve. Once we do that, everything flows positively."', '"Morning,Opportunity,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"When people are speaking, they require our undivided attention. We focus on them; we listen very carefully. We listen to the spoken words and the unspoken messages. This means looking directly at the person, eyes connected; we forget we have a watch, just focusing for that moment on that person."', '"Eyes,Moment,Focus"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Not long after I was married, World War II began. My husband John volunteered for the Navy and was sent to Pensacola for training as a Naval Combat Air Crew photographer. It seemed a strange assignment for a young newspaper editor and writer, already exempt, but off he went, saying goodbye to our 18-month-old Johnny and me."', '"War,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Leadership flows from inner character and integrity of ambition, which inspires others to lend themselves to your organization\'s mission."', '"Leadership,Character,Integrity"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"It takes courage for a leader to identify and confront self-imposed barriers, to put in place the personal strategies required to unleash the energy, innovation, and commitment to self-development."', '"Courage,Energy,Commitment"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Move beyond the old assumptions, practices, and language that can be barriers to equal access."', '"Language,Assumptions,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'We are increasingly becoming a pluralistic nation.', '"Nation,Becoming,Increasingly"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Management is the set of skills that can help get things done. Unfortunately, its practice is too often a bag of manipulative tricks to advance someone\'s own interests, which creates cynicism."', '"Bag,Practice,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"A single person doesn\'t change an organization, but culture and good people do."', '"Change,Good,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Tears belong within the family.', '"Family,Tears,Within"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I believe that tears should be very private, and no matter what issue or what situation, we should have a very dignified demeanor."', '"Believe,Tears,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"If you grow up in Germantown, Pennsylvania, as I did, 5:30 means 5:30."', '"Grow,Up,Did"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'There\'s something exhilarating about being in the mountains and talking about management and the future with Peter Drucker.', '"Future,Management,Talking"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"With a growing number of one-parent families in the country, the Girl Scout troop can be an indispensable and powerful positive factor."', '"Positive,Country,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"It is not business, it is not government - it is the social sector that may yet save the society."', '"Business,Society,Government"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Donors do not reward good intentions.', '"Good,Reward,Good Intentions"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'It is what we do with our lives that counts.', '"Counts,Our Lives,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Age is irrelevant.', '"Age,Irrelevant"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"At one time, there was a stereotype that your Girl Scout leader was the mother of a Brownie, but increasingly, we are having young businesswomen and professional women who are not mothers but care about children."', '"Women,Time,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Women are working for part or all of their adult lives now. The possibilities are limitless, but you need to prepare."', '"Women,Adult,Possibilities"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Selling cookies is usually a girl\'s first exposure to the world of business. She learns how to meet the public, talk about a product, sell the product, and is responsible for collecting money, giving change, and delivering the product. That\'s quite a business venture for a 7-year-old."', '"Change,Business,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I\'ll meet people and tell them what I do, and their first reaction is usually, \'Oh, I love Thin Mints!\' And you know, they are awfully good."', '"Love,Good,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"In my life, I don\'t have roadblocks and obstacles. I might have something you would call a \'challenge.\' I throw that out the window, and I call that a wonderful opportunity."', '"Life,Opportunity,Window"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'I did not want to take a troop. I was the mother of a little boy. I knew nothing about little girls.', '"Nothing,Boy,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I didn\'t have a career plan. But what I did was, whenever there was a door open and a new opportunity, I always looked into it and took a chance and walked through the door."', '"Chance,Opportunity,New"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"When I choose what I do, I ask, \'Does it make a difference?\'"', '"Make A Difference,Difference,Choose"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"One of the management imperatives in the \'90s is managing diversity. Whatever the organization, when the constituents of that organization look at the board and management staff, they need to find themselves."', '"Look,Diversity,Organization"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'The real leader redefines or defines the mission in a very powerful way so that people understand it; it permeates the organization.', '"Way,Organization,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"At a young age, I learned from my grandmother that I should respect all people. Her lessons were defining moments in my life and determined the type of leader that I would become."', '"Life,Respect,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'I thought I\'d never leave Pennsylvania. And I never imagined that I\'d one day have the chance to lead the largest organization for girls and women around the world.', '"Women,Chance,World"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"If you are building a corporate culture of greatness, you have to define culture on your own terms and with the people you work with."', '"Work,Culture,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"In 1976, I was invited to interview for the CEO position of the Girl Scouts of the U.S.A."', '"Interview,Position,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I never had any question about the direction we were going in at the Girl Scouts. We shared our mission and research with all levels of leaders from the very beginning - a concept I created, using cups and saucers, called \'circular management.\' Everyone was on a team; there were no superiors or subordinates. There was respect for all people."', '"Respect,Research,Direction"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'I always had this philosophy that only the best is good enough for those who serve girls.', '"Best,Good,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'I had read everything Peter Drucker ever wrote.', '"Everything,Had,Read"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'The Millennial mindset is one on the pulse of changing technology. They multi-task and enjoy a challenge. They need projects that utilize their knowledge and skills that can connect with their philosophical or deeper interests.', '"Knowledge,Technology,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Good leaders make people\'s strengths effective and their weaknesses irrelevant.', '"Good,People,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Dispirited, unmotivated, unappreciated workers cannot compete in a highly competitive world."', '"World,Cannot,Workers"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I lost my son in late 2011. He had been totally incapacitated from his neck down for the last eight years of his life, but his mind was alive and brilliant in those years. He even wrote a book, \'Allegheny Mountain,\' lying at home in his hospital bed."', '"Life,Home,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"I adored my grandparents and spent every weekend with Mama and Papa Wicks. They had seven children, so they needed a big house - and it seemed only logical to them to build into their house a pipe organ in a music room with a sixteen-foot ceiling."', '"Music,Children,Mama"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"In the future, it will not be the one big message, the one big voice, but millions of us, in our own way, healing, unifying, and experiencing that one defining moment when we recognize that sustaining the democracy is the common bottom line - whoever we are, whatever we do, wherever we are, the call is to sustain the democracy."', '"Future,Moment,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Girl Scouts helps girls make decisions that are right for them and offer support.', '"Support,Girl,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"We see change as a challenge, not as a threat."', '"Change,See,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'We cannot ensure equal access or build upon our diverse strengths by sitting at our desks.', '"Build,Sitting,Equal"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'Some corporations are extremely well managed; some nonprofit organizations are. It has nothing to do with the sector. It has to do with quality of management.', '"Quality,Nothing,Management"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"Simple questions can be profound, and answering them requires us to make stark and honest - and sometimes painful - self-assessments."', '"Simple,Sometimes,Questions"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', '"When it comes to communicating change at any time, the mission must be clear, and it must inspire."', '"Change,Time,Mission"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9d', 'There is just one reason that we are placed on this Earth. That reason is to love and be loved - in that order.', '"Love,Earth,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I\'m just fascinated by houses. In another life, I\'d have probably trained as an architect. If I had enough money, I\'d collect them like other people collect teapots. I don\'t know why I love them so much. I\'m just very interested in the idea of a house as a metaphor for the way one lives."', '"Life,Love,Money"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', 'What has impressed me the most about the Italians whose tables we\'ve sat at is that they are traditional cooks but also outrageously innovative. These people are wild improvisers.', '"Me,People,Wild"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I was born and grew up in Fitzgerald, way down in south Georgia. It was a mill town and my family ran the cotton mill. My grandfather was mayor many times and my family felt deeply rooted to that spot."', '"Family,Way,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I think I went to Italy initially for the art, architecture, food and history, but I stayed there because of the people in Cortona."', '"History,Art,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"If you\'ve got a plot the size of a car or a tiny yard in Italy, you\'re going to be growing tomatoes and basil and celery and carrots, and everybody is still connected to the land."', '"Car,Connected,Land"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I find that other countries have this or this, but Italy is the only one that has it all for me. The culture, the cuisine, the people, the landscape, the history. Just everything to me comes together there."', '"History,Together,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"Venice, the most touristy place in the world, is still just completely magic to me."', '"Me,World,Magic"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"The Italians have their priorities right: They\'re driven, they do their work, but they really enjoy the day-to-day and they don\'t put off the enjoyment of the everyday for some future goal."', '"Work,Future,Priorities"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I loved every place I lived and traveled. London, Paris, Rome, Venice. I fell hard for Central America and Mexico. In each country, I had fantasies that I could live there."', '"America,Country,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"Going to Europe as a budding cook opened my eyes to food in a different way. When I got to Italy, the first thing I did was put my little basil plants in the ground and watch them turn into big, healthy bushes."', '"Food,Eyes,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', 'It\'s kind of amazing that people will travel because of a book. I admire that.', '"Amazing,Travel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"When I was twelve, I started reading Eudora Welty, Thomas Wolfe, Flannery O\'Connor, James Agee, and - do we dare breathe the name - William Faulkner."', '"Name,Dare,Reading"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"Living in a small Italian hilltown, and having lived in a small town in south Georgia, I understand that you can recognize a family gene pool by the lift of an eyebrow, or the length of a neck, or a way of walking."', '"Family,Way,Walking"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"I got the idea that to write books would be the best way to spend a life. I never thought of anything else that seemed like half as much fun, although in my next life I would like to be an architect, too, so I can have an easier time restoring houses."', '"Life,Best,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"The longer you are in a place, the more you get under its layers."', '"Place,More,Layers"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"In America, people are just so straightforward when they dislike things."', '"America,People,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9e', '"When my husband is away and I\'m by myself, my neighbours will insist I eat with them every single night because they see it as unhealthy to eat by yourself."', '"Myself,Night,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'That\'s another great thing about getting older. Your life is written on your face.', '"Life,Great,Getting Older"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I was often told that I wasn\'t a thing. \'She\'s not pretty enough. She\'s not tall enough. She\'s not thin enough. She\'s not fat enough.\' I thought, \'O.K., someday you\'re going to be looking for someone not, not, not, not, and there I\'ll be.\'"', '"Looking,Fat,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"When you lose a spouse, you\'re a widow or widower; when you lose your parents, you\'re an orphan. When you lose a child, there\'s no word in the English language for that position, that place that you\'re left."', '"Lose,Parents,Orphan"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I think that there\'s a clinical mental illness called depression, but I believe that post-industrial America has been narcotized by progress. There\'s a cultural malaise - mental illness or no - that everybody suffers from at some point in their life."', '"Life,Progress,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I was too old, too young, too fat, too thin, too tall, too short, too blond, too dark - but at some point, they\'re going to need the other. So I\'d get really good at being the other."', '"Good,Fat,Dark"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My position has always been that the way people age and the signs that we show of aging is nature\'s way of tattooing. It\'s natural scarification, and the life you lead gives you the symbols and the emblems of your life, the road map you followed."', '"Life,Nature,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My name is Frances Louise McDormand, formerly known as Cynthia Ann Smith. I was born in Gibson City, Ill., in 1957. I identify as gender-normative, heterosexual, and white-trash American. My parents were not white trash. My birth mother was white trash."', '"City,Parents,White"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"With aging, you earn the right to be loyal to yourself."', '"Yourself,Aging,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'The only power you have is the word no.', '"Power,Only,Word"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"The last scene in \'Moonlight,\' that\'s one of the most extraordinary things I\'ve ever seen on film in my lifetime. You see two men showing such tenderness towards each other. And it\'s bold; it\'s deep. It\'s complex. It\'s profound."', '"Men,Moonlight,Bold"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'m not an actor because I want my picture taken. I\'m an actor because I want to be part of the human exchange.', '"Picture,Human,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'The fact that I\'m sleeping with the director may have something to do with it.', '"Something,May,Director"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I am an ordinary person.', '"I Am,Person,Ordinary Person"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Here\'s what I have at my advantage: I\'ve never been a personality. I\'ve always been a character actor.', '"Personality,Character,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I never trusted good-looking boys.', '"Trust,Never,Good-Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Because of my own insecurities about the way I look, I do sometimes sabotage the looks of my characters by making them as homely as possible. I\'ve never done a glamour part. I\'d like to some day, though I don\'t know if I could pull it off."', '"Look,Day,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I learned how to read in second grade, and I entered a summer contest at my local library in Chattanooga, Tennessee. If you read more books than anybody else, you got your Polaroid up on the bulletin board, and I did."', '"Summer,Library,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Guess what? I am an ordinary person.', '"I Am,Person,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'m a character actress, plain and simple... Who can worry about a career? Have a life. Movie stars have careers - actors work, and then they don\'t work, and then they work again."', '"Life,Work,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"If you want to talk about cultural appropriation, we have to go back to the Greeks."', '"Back,Talk,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"If you take it as a compliment that you don\'t look your age, then you\'re really shooting yourself in the foot."', '"Age,Look,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I know I\'m profane. And outspoken.', '"Know,Outspoken,Profane"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I think that ageism is a cultural illness; it\'s not a personal illness.', '"Personal,Illness,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'It\'s much easier to play supporting roles because that\'s what I do in my life: I support my son.', '"Life,Support,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I don\'t think of myself as a movie star and I can pretty easily convince other people that I\'m not a movie star.', '"Myself,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I will go to my grave being known as Marge Gunderson. It\'ll be on my gravestone if I have one. I don\'t mind that, because it was a great character."', '"Great,Character,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"A 90-minute time frame is not long enough to tell a good female story, and that\'s why long-format television has become so great for female storytelling and for female performers and directors and writers."', '"Time,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Female characters in literature are full. They\'re messy: they\'ve got runny noses and burp and belch. Unfortunately, in film, female characters don\'t often have that kind of richness."', '"Literature,Messy,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I want to be revered. I want to be an elder; I want to be an elderess.', '"Want,Revered,Elder"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I don\'t think you can ever completely transform yourself on film, but if you do your job well, you can make people believe that you\'re the character you\'re trying to be."', '"Character,Believe,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I swear a lot; I always have. So does my husband. Our son, surprisingly, does not swear much at all."', '"Son,Always,Husband"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"At least three times a week, I\'m approached by someone who says something about \'Fargo.\'"', '"Three,Week,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I think awards are good for the movie. They can bring a new audience to the movie. I\'ve always claimed that things like that don\'t get you work. Work gets you work. That\'s my blue-collar, protestant work ethic."', '"Work,Good,New"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'ve made a professional reputation playing working-class, middle-class, American women. There\'s a real sense of stoicism and pragmatism and strength and lyricism of a woman like that."', '"Strength,Women,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My politics are private, but many of my feminist politics cross over into my professional life."', '"Life,Politics,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Growing up a preacher\'s kid wasn\'t the easiest thing. Everybody\'s always watching you to see how you\'ll behave - or misbehave.', '"See,Watching,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'m not a depressive, but I certainly have mood swings. It\'s an occupational hazard, I would say, and I\'m glad I\'m in the occupation I\'m in."', '"Mood,Mood Swings,Glad"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Most women\'s pictures are as boring and as formulaic as men\'s pictures. In place of a car chase or a battle scene, what you get is an extreme closeup of a woman breaking down."', '"Car,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Everybody dresses like a teenager. Everybody dyes their hair. Everybody is concerned about a smooth face.', '"Face,Hair,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I have not mutated myself in any way.', '"Myself,Way,Any"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I went to my school careers counselors and said I wanted to be an actor, and they didn\'t know what to do. They showed me catalogues with pretty campuses and said, \'Oh, look, there\'s a theater building. Why don\'t you go there?\'"', '"Look,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I like hard rock, and classic rock, and even metal."', '"Rock,Hard,Metal"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I haven\'t wanted to play a mother for a long time because I am one.', '"Time,Long,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Certainly, a lot of the films I\'ve worked on have ended up good movies, but they haven\'t always been the best experiences."', '"Best,Good,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Movie stars have careers - actors work, and then they don\'t work, and then they work again."', '"Work,Stars,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"It\'s a scary thing going into the workforce with a $50,000 debt and you\'ve been trained as a classical theatre actor. There\'s always a depression in the theatre."', '"Always,Depression,Theatre"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"There\'s only two givens with choosing acting as a profession: one is you will always be unemployed, always, and it doesn\'t matter how much money you make, you\'re still always going to be unemployed; and that you have no power."', '"Money,Power,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'m trained in the theater, and acting, for me, is about the imaginative life I create for myself, not about basing it on something real. I think that whatever I create becomes the reality for the audience."', '"Life,Myself,Reality"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I was completely naive about the business of being an actor. My family didn\'t go to the theater or to the movies. We watched television like every 1960s small-town American family, and I certainly never thought about being on TV. I thought I was going to be a classical actor in the grand tradition."', '"Family,Business,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I became interested in educating people in the variety of ways in which women can express their emotion. Which is much easier to do in a large role than in a supporting role to a male protagonist. In general, the women in a supporting role to a male protagonist - cry a lot."', '"Women,People,Cry"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'m not really that interested in going back to playing small supporting roles.', '"Back,Small,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"The crew on \'Three Bilboards,\' by the way, is one of the best I\'ve ever worked with. And that\'s not hyperbole."', '"Best,Way,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'m from working-class, blue-collar America, and I don\'t believe that people in that socioeconomic strata wait until they\'re 40 to have children."', '"Believe,Wait,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Something happened culturally: No one is supposed to age past 45 - sartorially, cosmetically, attitudinally."', '"Age,Past,Happened"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'We are on red alert when it comes to how we are perceiving ourselves as a species. There\'s no desire to be an adult.', '"Red,Desire,Adult"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Adulthood is not a goal. It\'s not seen as a gift.', '"Gift,Adulthood,Seen"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Getting older and adjusting to all the things that biologically happen to you is not easy to do and is a constant struggle and adjustment.', '"Struggle,Getting Older,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'We don\'t need a lot of initiatives for women in film; what we need is money.', '"Women,Money,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'One of the reasons I am successful as a producer is that I\'ve been a very successful housewife.', '"I Am,Housewife,Producer"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'All the skills of housewifery are the ones I\'m using as a producer.', '"Skills,Producer,Using"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Unfortunately, any girl - unless you\'re playing the action hero - is going to end up at some point handcuffed, gagged, and waiting for the hero to save her."', '"Waiting,Hero,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I portray female characters, so I have the opportunity to change the way people look at them. Even if I wasn\'t consciously doing that, it would happen anyway just because of how I present as a woman, or as a person. I present in a way that\'s not stereotypical, even if I\'m playing a stereotypical role."', '"Change,Opportunity,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I went to high school in a steel town in Pennsylvania.', '"School,Steel,High School"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"It\'s like some weird excuse for high school kids to vomit. It\'s not good. It\'s stupid. I\'m sure that\'s not what St. Patrick\'s Day is supposed to be about, but who knows."', '"Good,Stupid,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Even though I\'m an actor, I\'ve gone to productions where there has been someone whose work is known in film, and you can\'t take your eyes off them. It unbalances the production. Whether they\'re good or not, it doesn\'t matter."', '"Work,Good,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Yale? I was at Yale on a scholarship.', '"Scholarship,Yale"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Unless I\'m on a stage, I don\'t want to be the event in someone\'s day."', '"Day,Stage,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"It\'s kind of a subversive act to tell a story of a woman past a certain age, to develop a four-hour movie based on a marriage and a story of two people past middle age."', '"Age,Marriage,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Long-format television is a better way to tell a female story.', '"Better,Way,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I am not a director or a writer, but a filmmaker."', '"I Am,Director,Filmmaker"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I read books. Remember those? I read them, on paper."', '"Remember,Paper,Books"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I buy books, I have shelves of books. I love to read."', '"Love,Buy,Books"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I have a very short attention span.', '"Attention,Attention Span,Short"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'It was really fascinating for everyone involved in \'Fargo\' that Marge Gunderson became the iconic character she did. I think it was something about the cultural zeitgeist and what was happening with women in the workplace.', '"Women,Character,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"In comparison to other women in the world, perhaps I\'m seen as smaller. But I\'ve never had a problem thinking of myself as a large woman."', '"Women,Myself,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I think that cosmetic enhancements in my profession are just an occupational hazard. But I think, more culturally, I\'m interested in starting the conversation about aging gracefully and how, instead of making it a cultural problem, we make it individuals\' problems."', '"Problems,Conversation,Aging"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'It could be partly my taste. It\'s just my belief that there are female characters that will benefit from not being vulnerable.', '"Will,Belief,Taste"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'There\'s something healing about tears.', '"Tears,Healing,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'m not really interested in promoting \'Olive\' as a series about depression or mental illness.', '"Depression,Illness,Mental Illness"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"In my theater work, I\'ve had much more three-dimensional, broader-stroke characters."', '"Work,More,Three-Dimensional"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'m really interested in playing my age.', '"Age,Playing,Interested"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I like being my age. I kind of have a political thing about it.', '"Age,Political,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'ve always known that I\'ll have a career for the rest of my life because they\'ll always make movies about men, and men need women in their lives. But, when it comes to telling a woman\'s story, they\'re complex, circular, and not genre-driven."', '"Life,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"We wrote \'Olive Kitteridge\' as six hours, and they asked us to make it in four."', '"Four,Us,Olive"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('394999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My son smelled like a cinnamon bun, and that smell entered into my biological being, and it became an imperative that I keep him alive at all costs, so then there\'s this monster - this tiger or lion - that comes forward in you to protect them. And it doesn\'t stop. It doesn\'t matter if they become men or women."', '"Women,Men,Tiger"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My father was a minister, and it was more my mother that had the responsibility of making sure the family put out an outward of appearance of living what he was preaching. She was the PR."', '"Family,Responsibility,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I never read books - and still don\'t read books - to develop them.', '"Never,Develop,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'ve given just as much of my life to that, and I practiced it with the same zeal, as I have acting. And I think that many of my skill sets from being a housewife I used for producing. Because you don\'t stop until it\'s done."', '"Life,Skill,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I\'ve got a rubber face. It has always served me very well and really helps, especially as I get older, because I still have all my road map intact, and I can use it at will."', '"Face,Me,Road"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'There is simply too much of my life that is involved in my work that I couldn\'t replicate in any other way.', '"Life,Work,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I tried taking a year off when Pedro was a toddler because I really wanted to be around, but it wasn\'t good for any of us."', '"Good,Us,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"My feminist training was that this was your goal, to be a self-sufficient woman, but that is a miscalculation. It\'s just not the way we work. We work in dialogue with the community."', '"Work,Community,Training"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'m attracted to male gestures and sexuality.', '"Sexuality,Gestures,Attracted"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I\'ve never been someone who needs a lot of takes or enjoys a lot of takes. I like the fast thing of it.', '"Fast,Never,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I love flying by the seat of my pants, going at something instinctually."', '"Love,Flying,Seat"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"You can\'t make a rule about it. The minute you make a rule, it\'s like putting your wedding pictures in \'In Style\' magazine - you\'re divorced."', '"Wedding,Style,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I have friends who are movie stars, and I think it\'s just as hard a job as being a working actor. But it\'s a different job, and it\'s not the one I want."', '"Stars,Hard,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"If, when I leave this earth, I\'m remembered for \'Fargo,\' so be it. But I think old Marge Gunderson is gonna get a run for her money with Olive Kittredge."', '"Money,Earth,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'People love to drop in \'you betcha\' as often as they can.', '"Love,People,Drop"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"KWMR is my radio station, and I intend to have a job there as I get older. That\'s what I\'m lobbying for. They don\'t need me. They\'ve got plenty of people. But let\'s see if I can make myself indispensable."', '"Myself,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I haven\'t done much press for many reasons, but mostly because it\'s not an interesting dialogue about work that\'s been done. It\'s turned into something else. It\'s become this ridiculous other thing."', '"Work,Done,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I was very good until I left home to go to a little college in West Virginia, and then I started to break some rules."', '"Good,Home,Rules"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"I wasn\'t into sports, but I was really into Shakespeare."', '"Sports,Really,Shakespeare"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'We appreciate quiet living. It\'s not exactly a Hollywood way of life - I couldn\'t stand living out in Hollywood because you can never escape from the business. All people ever do is talk about movies. At least in New York you can have some other life.', '"Life,Business,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I want to separate my professional life from my personal life. I want to live a normal life and be a normal mother.', '"Life,Live,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'No actor has complete freedom.', '"Freedom,Actor,Complete"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'What\'s wrong with Hell\'s Kitchen? You don\'t change a neighborhood by changing its name. You change it by building a school.', '"Change,Hell,School"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I can\'t do the frappuccino. It\'s too sweet. I need it straight.', '"Sweet,Need,Straight"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'Cinematic icons of the police detective are more male role models than female.', '"Police,More,Role"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I would disagree that America is any more racist or ridiculous than anywhere else.', '"America,More,Ridiculous"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'I can do a good John Wayne.', '"Good,I Can,John"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', '"Unless it\'s a flat-out farce, an actor can\'t play comedy on film."', '"Comedy,Film,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'You just have to play the character.', '"Character,Play,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fd9f', 'A movie set actually can be a good place to have a family atmosphere.', '"Family,Good,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', 'Being a woman has only bothered me in climbing trees.', '"Me,Woman,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"But with the slow menace of a glacier, depression came on. No one had any measure of its progress; no one had any plan for stopping it. Everyone tried to get out of its way."', '"Progress,Way,Slow"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"The door might not be opened to a woman again for a long, long time, and I had a kind of duty to other women to walk in and sit down on the chair that was offered, and so establish the right of others long hence and far distant in geography to sit in the high seats."', '"Women,Time,Walk"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"The quality of his being one with the people, of having no artificial or natural barriers between him and them, made it possible for him to be a leader without ever being or thinking of being a dictator."', '"Thinking,Quality,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"To one who believes that really good industrial conditions are the hope for a machine civilization, nothing is more heartening than to watch conference methods and education replacing police methods."', '"Education,Hope,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"In America, public opinion is the leader."', '"America,Opinion,Leader"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda2', '"Most of man\'s problems upon this planet, in the long history of the race, have been met and solved either partially or as a whole by experiment based on common sense and carried out with courage."', '"History,Courage,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m not perfect. But I hold myself to a high standard every day.', '"Myself,Not Perfect,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Clay... is my favorite surface.', '"Clay,Surface,Favorite"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"He\'s an absolute icon. Everything he brings, how he carries himself. Never having trouble with the media, never done anything wrong. He\'s a superstar for a reason. He\'s LeBron James for a reason."', '"Media,Done,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"When I met Jay-Z and Beyonce I was in awe, stuttering like crazy. This guy grew up in the projects and he and Beyonce are a billionaire couple. The empires they\'ve built, affecting so many lives, is unbelievable."', '"Crazy,Empires,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"While turning pro had a lot of upside, for me, it could also have turned out to be a disaster."', '"Me,Disaster,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"My mom, she wanted me to go to college and then after that you could do what you want."', '"Mom,Me,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I know it\'s a cliche to say, \'There isn\'t anything you can\'t do if you believe,\' but that\'s something I subscribe to, even if it\'s corny."', '"Believe,Know,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Look, I\'m not saying you can\'t make it if you grew up from a wealthy situation. I mean, a ton of people have."', '"Look,People,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"If anything, you just let your racket talk - there\'s no reason for you to talk if your racket can."', '"Talk,Anything,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'ve had signs I can play at the highest level.', '"I Can,Signs,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m a pretty good problem solver.', '"Good,Pretty,Problem"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I want to win titles like Delray and even bigger.', '"Win,Want,Bigger"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I obviously wasn\'t a normal tennis story.', '"Tennis,Story,Normal"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'How many years have I been watching the U.S. Open? Since I was a little kid.', '"Watching,Open,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I always dreamed of being on center court, playing the best in the world."', '"Best,World,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'ve been playing against really good guys. Put myself in positions to win. Eventually I\'ll win more than I lose these.', '"Good,Myself,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'For a while I feel like I can play against anyone in the world.', '"World,Feel,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Being back home is a great thing for me, being with my family, being with friends, being with people that have got your back no matter what."', '"Family,Home,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"It\'s good to bring a different feel to tennis, and that\'s what I feel like I bring. I bring a different feel, a different swagger to tennis. I\'m very easygoing, and very nonchalant, it looks like, when I\'m out there - I\'ve got a little strut, and I like that."', '"Good,Feel,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I have that balance of having fun - because I can need to have a ton of fun - but also locking it in at times.', '"Fun,Balance,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"There\'s no reason trying to fit in: Just be you. That was the biggest thing for me, just being me, and finding what works for me."', '"Me,Trying,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m putting constant pressure on my opponents and really dictating play.', '"Pressure,Play,Constant"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m really trying to understand my game.', '"Game,Trying,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Obviously, Jay Z definitely got my attention. I thought it was pretty cool that he wanted me on the team."', '"Cool,Me,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'To get a former player that has been there and has that extra intel. Jose Higueras is a great coach for that and a great person as well.', '"Great,Person,Great Person"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Anybody plays a good match, you can beat anybody on a given day."', '"Good,Day,Beat"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I need to get a lot better.', '"Better,Need,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Obviously it\'s how bad do you really want to be successful, essentially. Like, what does that really mean to you? Why are you doing it?"', '"Bad,Doing,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Tennis needs some different personalities and a lot more emotions.', '"Emotions,Tennis,More"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Guys are so good. It\'s just about how badly you want it. I want it real bad.', '"Good,Bad,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It\'s all about competing.', '"About,Competing"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I\'m going for the big moments - I want the big moments. I just tell myself, \'Remember the work you did, the things you went through. And keep going.\'"', '"Work,Myself,Keep Going"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Obviously, maturity helps, knowing that you definitely have to make every day a good day. If not, somebody else is out there putting in the work."', '"Work,Good,Good Day"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I maximize every day.', '"Day,Every Day,Every"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"To see my brother, see my friends, I think it builds character for me, just being accountable for myself."', '"Myself,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"It really shaped me as a person going to DeMatha. Anyone that plays athletics or does music or does whatever, it teaches them to work to the best of their abilities."', '"Work,Best,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It\'s not like everything was given to me. I had to really work hard for it and earn it.', '"Work,Me,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'ve been on a tennis court all my life. The only thing that\'s been there longer is the net post.', '"Life,My Life,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m very thankful for what I have. I don\'t want to let anyone down.', '"Thankful,Down,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I think about all the kids that look up to me now... Things are possible if you go get it.', '"Look,Me,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I was lucky; I got so many opportunities.', '"Lucky,Got,Opportunities"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I know in the back of my head I have a Grand Slam win, which definitely takes a lot off of me, a big load off."', '"Me,Win,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I learned that I could definitely play at a really high level and I definitely belong at this level.', '"High,Play,High Level"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I just got to keep competing and keep believing.', '"Believing,Just,Keep"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It\'s an honor to play on the same team as some of the best players in the history of the game.', '"Best,History,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I think winning at Wimbledon\'s huge. This is the biggest tournament in tennis for so many different reasons. You can see the history around the grounds. The Village around you, everyone lives for it."', '"History,Village,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"People outside of tennis, all the famous actors and everyone, knows Wimbledon."', '"Famous,People,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'All credit to Robby Ginepri. He\'s helped me a lot.', '"Me,Credit,He"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'This is what I\'ve always wanted to do. I\'ve always wanted to be a professional tennis player.', '"Always,Professional,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I knew I was going to play pro tennis when I was 12.', '"Tennis,Play,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Tennis is my life.', '"Life,My Life,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I never try to get ahead of myself because there\'s nothing that bothers me more than cockiness. I don\'t think that\'s necessary at all.', '"Myself,Me,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I want to take initiative; I know my game and I know what I need to do to win.', '"Game,Win,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"If you stop working hard, that\'s when things get to your head."', '"Stop,Hard,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m trying to... stay humble and keep doing what I do.', '"Humble,Doing,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Without my dad doing what he did, and without me putting in the hours, there wouldn\'t be any travelling the world or playing with the pros. He\'s a huge part of it."', '"Dad,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'My goal isn\'t to be a top junior. It\'s to be a top pro.', '"Top,Goal,Pro"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I just wanted to play and play and play. When everyone left, I\'d stay on the court and hit serves or play against the wall."', '"Everyone,Stay,Court"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I mean, sometimes you have to go to work."', '"Work,Sometimes,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It doesn\'t really matter who I turn pro with. What matters is where I take my tennis.', '"Matter,Tennis,Turn"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I\'m pretty close with a majority of the black tennis players.', '"Black,Tennis,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Davis Cup helped me a lot. Being in that great atmosphere and having the chance to hit with top 50 guys everyday, being on the practice courts, that gave me a lot of confidence."', '"Great,Chance,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"From the ground, I\'m pretty solid from both sides. My form really helps me a lot and my backend complements it."', '"Me,Ground,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I think my serve and trying to come forward a little more are what I need to work on.', '"Work,Trying,More"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"You start to take those opportunities when you do get a wildcard, but also you\'re allowed to say no - just because you get a wildcard doesn\'t mean you have to say yes. Some weeks I think its OK to take a wildcard, some weeks its not."', '"Start,Just Because,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'All these pros are getting better every day. You just want to catch up to them.', '"Day,Better,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Some days, obviously, I am like \'Today is not the day,\' but you got to push through, especially when my aspirations are to be pro, you can\'t have any bad days."', '"Today,I Am,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"USTA helps me out a lot, the Tennis Center. I can\'t thank them enough."', '"Me,Enough,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Being the number one seed, you\'re thinking you don\'t want to lose in the second round."', '"Thinking,Lose,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Playing in a main draw Grand Slam is something you dream about as a kid.', '"Dream,Something,About"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It\'s hard to win Grand Slams.', '"Win,Hard,Grand"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'There are a bunch of young players coming up and doing incredible stuff.', '"Doing,Young,Coming"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'Hopefully my era can help build the game.', '"Game,Help,Build"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I don\'t let it get to my head because there have been plenty of good juniors that haven\'t made it to the big stage.', '"Good,Big,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I don\'t want to be playing on Court 17 for the rest of my life.', '"Life,My Life,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I think Kevin Durant being that humble is huge.', '"Humble,Think,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Since I was like eight, I always wanted to be playing pro tennis."', '"Always,Tennis,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"When I told people that I wanted to grow up to be a tennis player, they laughed at me. My dad has always been supportive, but he was laughing, too."', '"Dad,Me,Grow"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"The U.S. Open is so special, and I\'m not even saying that as an American. I just can\'t envision a better atmosphere."', '"Better,American,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'My mom actively did not want me to play professionally.', '"Mom,Me,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I was born into a poor family but my family\'s good. I\'m good and I\'m going to do something great.', '"Family,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Serena\'s arguably the best athlete of all time, so getting to know her was surreal."', '"Best,Time,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It was not until I got sponsored at 12 that I finally owned a racket.', '"Finally,Got,Racket"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"The thing is, everybody wants to be famous. Everybody wants to be successful. Everybody wants to be that dude, but not everybody wants to do the work for it. And I think that\'s probably one of the reasons why there\'s so many juniors and only a couple that make it. Because I really wanted it. I wanted it real bad."', '"Work,Famous,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I want young kids to play tennis because of me.', '"Me,Young,Tennis"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I want to really change people\'s lives with what I do for a living.', '"Change,People,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"People in tennis, they\'ve been in a certain bubble for so long they don\'t even know who they are, because obviously it\'s just been tennis, tennis, tennis. And let it be just tennis, tennis, tennis. Be locked into that. But when tennis is done, then what? It\'s kinda like: Let\'s enjoy being great at the sport."', '"Great,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"There was always a purpose in what I did on the court because at the end of the day, my parents, they sacrificed for me and my brother. I had to do it for them."', '"End Of The Day,Me,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"As far as myself, I want to see myself hold a Grand Slam, be at the top of the game."', '"Myself,Game,See"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"Love the people that want to support you, love the people who are there for you, because you definitely earned that right."', '"Love,Support,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'My parents were hardworking and still are. Everything I do is for them and the family.', '"Family,Parents,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I don\'t think our priority should be on immigrants. Obviously, they come to the States for a better life, so the last thing they want to do is rob a bank or do something bad."', '"Life,Bad,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'You can\'t forget your roots.', '"Roots,Forget,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I try to treat everyone with love and respect. If you do that, you get the same back, if not more."', '"Love,Respect,Treat"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I had a lot of Pokemon Pikachu t-shirts on court and hand-me-downs from other kids.', '"Court,Kids,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"My academy did a great job of getting my story out there for people to hear about me, get interested and wanted to fund me."', '"Great,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'I just want to be great.', '"Great,Want,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I\'ve played so many matches in my career so far where I played unbelievable, came up just short."', '"Far,Short,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', 'It\'s Roger Federer - this guy has about a million Grand Slams and done everything.', '"Done,Everything,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda3', '"I have fun when it\'s the right time to have fun, but when I lock in for practice and matches, I\'m not worried about fun."', '"Time,Fun,Practice"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Equality is the soul of liberty; there is, in fact, no liberty without it."', '"Equality,Soul,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"All that I say is, examine, inquire. Look into the nature of things. Search out the grounds of your opinions, the for and against. Know why you believe, understand what you believe, and possess a reason for the faith that is in you."', '"Nature,Faith,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Pets, like their owners, tend to expand a little over the Christmas period."', '"Christmas,Like,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Surely it is time to examine into the meaning of words and the nature of things, and to arrive at simple facts, not received upon the dictum of learned authorities, but upon attentive personal observation of what is passing around us."', '"Nature,Time,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Do we exert our own liberties without injury to others - we exert them justly; do we exert them at the expense of others - unjustly. And, in thus doing, we step from the sure platform of liberty upon the uncertain threshold of tyranny."', '"Step,Liberty,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"It will appear evident upon attentive consideration that equality of intellectual and physical advantages is the only sure foundation of liberty, and that such equality may best, and perhaps only, be obtained by a union of interests and cooperation in labor."', '"Best,Equality,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Now here is a departure from the first principle of true ethics. Here we find ideas of moral wrong and moral right associated with something else than beneficial action. The consequent is, we lose sight of the real basis of morals, and substitute a false one."', '"Lose,Action,Ethics"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"He who lives in the single exercise of his mental faculties, however usefully or curiously directed, is equally an imperfect animal with the man who knows only the exercise of muscles."', '"Man,Exercise,Animal"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', 'The sciences have ever been the surest guides to virtue.', '"Virtue,Been,Guides"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Religion may be defined thus: a belief in, and homage rendered to, existences unseen and causes unknown."', '"Religion,Belief,Unknown"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"The existing principle of selfish interest and competition has been carried to its extreme point; and, in its progress, has isolated the heart of man, blunted the edge of his finest sensibilities, and annihilated all his most generous impulses and sympathies."', '"Heart,Progress,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Know why you believe, understand what you believe, and possess a reason for the faith that is in you."', '"Faith,Believe,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Let us unite on the safe and sure ground of fact and experiment, and we can never err; yet better, we can never differ."', '"Better,Safe,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"A necessary consequent of religious belief is the attaching ideas of merit to that belief, and of demerit to its absence."', '"Ideas,Belief,Absence"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Awaken its powers, and it will respect itself."', '"Respect,Will,Awaken"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', 'And when did mere preaching do any good? Put something in the place of these things. Fill the vacuum of the mind.', '"Good,Mind,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"But while human liberty has engaged the attention of the enlightened, and enlisted the feelings of the generous of all civilized nations, may we not enquire if this liberty has been rightly understood?"', '"Feelings,Liberty,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"If they exert it not for good, they will for evil; if they advance not knowledge, they will perpetuate ignorance."', '"Knowledge,Good,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Instead of establishing facts, we have to overthrow errors; instead of ascertaining what is, we have to chase from our imaginations what is not."', '"Facts,Chase,Errors"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Look into the nature of things. Search out the grounds of your opinions, the for and against."', '"Nature,Look,Search"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', 'Man has been adjudged a social animal.', '"Man,Animal,Social"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Our religious belief usurps the place of our sensations, our imaginations of our judgment. We no longer look to actions, trace their consequences, and then deduce the rule; we first make the rule, and then, right or wrong, force the action to square with it."', '"Look,Action,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"Speak of change, and the world is in alarm. And yet where do we not see change?"', '"Change,World,See"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"The hired preachers of all sects, creeds, and religions, never do, and never can, teach any thing but what is in conformity with the opinions of those who pay them."', '"Never,Conformity,Opinions"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"The simplest principles become difficult of practice, when habits, formed in error, have been fixed by time, and the simplest truths hard to receive when prejudice has warped the mind."', '"Time,Mind,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"We have seen that no religion stands on the basis of things known; none bounds its horizon within the field of human observation; and, therefore, as it can never present us with indisputable facts, so must it ever be at once a source of error and contention."', '"Religion,Facts,Horizon"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"We hear of the wealth of nations, of the powers of production, of the demand and supply of markets, and we forget that these words mean no more, if they mean any thing, then the happiness, and the labor, and the necessities of men."', '"Happiness,Men,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', 'There is but one honest limit to the rights of a sentient being; it is where they touch the rights of another sentient being.', '"Touch,Limit,Rights"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"These will vary in every human being; but knowledge is the same for every mind, and every mind may and ought to be trained to receive it."', '"Knowledge,Mind,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"It is in vain that we would circumscribe the power of one half of our race, and that half by far the most important and influential."', '"Power,Important,Race"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"If we bring not the good courage of minds covetous of truth, and truth only, prepared to hear all things, and decide upon all things, according to evidence, we should do more wisely to sit down contented in ignorance, than to bestir ourselves only to reap disappointment."', '"Truth,Courage,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"However novel it may appear, I shall venture the assertion, that, until women assume the place in society which good sense and good feeling alike assign to them, human improvement must advance but feebly."', '"Women,Good,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda4', '"How are men to be secured in any rights without instruction; how to be secured in the equal exercise of those rights without equality of instruction? By instruction understand me to mean knowledge - just knowledge; not talent, not genius, not inventive mental powers."', '"Knowledge,Men,Equality"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"However successful you are, there is no substitute for a close relationship. We all need them."', '"Relationship,Dating,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Eat well and sleep well. That will feed your nervous system and your psyche. As you get older, you look how you feel."', '"Look,Sleep,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:50:00', '2023-05-29 11:50:00'),
	('395171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'m one of the great unemployed looking for the next job. I\'m waiting for the right offer. Like anyone, I want something that turns me on inside."', '"Great,Waiting,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"The minute anyone\'s getting anxious I say, You must eat and you must sleep. They\'re the two vital elements for a healthy life."', '"Life,Health,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I have yet to see a drama that puts forward women who are successful and also have a family... they are nearly always seen as victims.', '"Family,Women,Drama"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I have always done exercise because I was a dancer, and it is probably good for you. I have done yoga consistently."', '"Good,Exercise,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"In Europe, we admire grown-up women; I think men revere older women."', '"Women,Men,Admire"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I am not going to share my private life with millions of people. I don\'t find a need to do that and nobody else close to me does either.', '"Life,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I don\'t want three million people digesting my private life over their cornflakes.', '"Life,Private Life,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"We all know now that people can look good for their age. It isn\'t so extraordinary, I don\'t know why people go on about it so much."', '"Good,Age,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"As you grow older, your whole life becomes very rich, multifaceted."', '"Life,Grow,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I come from a very hospitable, close, Catholic, matriarchal family."', '"Family,Come,Close"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"From one till seven, when we moved to England, I spoke only Portuguese. But I can\'t speak a word of it now."', '"Speak,Now,Seven"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'m trying to learn to smoke, which is rather weird when everyone is trying to stop. I\'m not a smoker. But my character only smokes as an affectation."', '"Character,Smoke,Weird"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'m not bothered or sad about being on my own - after all, I\'ve never had a husband."', '"Sad,Never,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Having children with someone is the real bond.', '"Parenting,Bond,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'The first thing you have to do is accept that decay sets in and there\'s nothing you can do about it.', '"Nothing,Accept,First"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I think people should do whatever they want to do. That\'s the point. Why should you care what other people think or say? You\'re not living in their pocket.', '"Care,People,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I\'ve always kept fit but I\'ve been doing gym and yoga and will be throwing my stilettoes away for a while!', '"Will,Doing,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I like having a good time. It\'s probably my mother\'s Brazilian genes in me - party, party."', '"Time,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'You have to be careful not to let your fear stop you doing things. It\'s very exciting to test yourself.', '"Fear,Yourself,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I don\'t regret the passing of time. I try to live in the present, which should mean my life\'s full."', '"Life,Time,Regret"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I am not a fanatic about anything. I do what I can do when I\'ve got the time.', '"Time,I Am,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'The funny thing is I\'m not bothered or sad about being on my own - after all I\'ve never had a husband.', '"Funny,Sad,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Judi Dench and Ian McKellen taught me how to work hard and respect the theatre.', '"Work,Respect,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I don\'t believe in expending energy on something you can\'t do anything about. If there was some easy way of fixing things, I\'d probably do it."', '"Believe,Energy,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I can easily sleep from nine to 13 hours a night.', '"Night,Sleep,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I maintain the rather old-fashioned view that this is my work and it\'s in the public arena, but that doesn\'t entitle everyone to know what happened at home before coming here."', '"Work,Home,View"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Everything has changed. An interview has become such a confrontational thing. It makes you very defensive.', '"Everything,Interview,Become"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I am pretty self-indulgent.', '"I Am,Pretty,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I can feel the 60S looming. In my profession, I\'ve just moved along with my age. By thinking in decades, rather than whether someone\'s 42 or 47, you can give yourself a whole 10 years to turn yourself around in."', '"Age,Thinking,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I consulted a Chinese herbalist and spent two weeks on an island off the coast of Zanzibar. I was away from any kind of contemporary technology.', '"Technology,Island,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I couldn\'t imagine playing someone young now; it would be so boring.', '"Boring,Young,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I didn\'t choose to be an actress.', '"Choose,Actress"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I do find acting cathartic.', '"Acting,Find,Cathartic"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I do think it\'s important to live in the present because in that way you won\'t be living in a state of regret.', '"Regret,Way,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I don\'t buy the tabloids, but you\'re surrounded by it all and people tell you things they\'ve read. I\'d be sitting on a train looking over someone\'s shoulder and thinking: That\'s familiar... oh my God, it\'s me."', '"God,Thinking,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I don\'t need a piece of paper to suggest that I can commit myself.', '"Myself,I Can,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I go on giving interviews because I\'ve been brought up to support the projects I\'m involved in. When you\'ve enjoyed working on a production, you want to do them a favour."', '"Support,Go,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I have made a public statement about me and Ralph by being seen with him. I don\'t need to make any other. You can live the way you want.', '"Me,Way,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I think people have surgery for psychological reasons more than because of their looks.', '"People,More,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I used to suffer from excessive pride. Well, I got over that one."', '"Pride,Well,Over"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I was asked to be in Vogue but I said no. I didn\'t want to advertise make-up. I didn\'t want to be seen as a sex symbol.', '"Sex,Want,Seen"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I\'ll dance to anything: Bob Marley or rap.', '"Dance,Anything,Rap"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'m an actress, not a pinup."', 'Actress', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'m often asked if I regret not going to Hollywood. I\'m glad I didn\'t go, because if I had I wouldn\'t have my extended family, which is the fabric of my life. Only recently have I realised how special and unusual it is."', '"Life,Family,Regret"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I\'ve never been married and I\'ve no more desire to be married now than I ever have. I hate bureaucracy and I am not religious.', '"Hate,I Am,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"If people think I look good, it\'s the make-up."', '"Good,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Roman\'s wife Sharon Tate had been murdered by Charles Manson the year before, but Roman had been through so much leaving the Warsaw ghetto that he was very strong and private."', '"Wife,Ghetto,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Some actors get fired up by the sound of the audience. I just want to retreat.', '"Sound,Audience,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Sometimes sushi is just superb, and other times there\'s nothing like a great big steak. It depends where your taste buds are at the time."', '"Time,Great,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Thank God we\'re not like America. Everyone wants to look like they\'re 20. In Europe we admire grown-up women; I think men revere older women.', '"God,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'The thing about doing anything artificial to your hair is that you have to look after it. So you\'re always vulnerable to the weather and time.', '"Time,Weather,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"The wonderful thing about acting is you move along with your decade. The older you get, the more interesting the parts you get to play and you bring more of your personal experience to the part."', '"Experience,Acting,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'There is not enough celebration of companionship. Relationships aren\'t just about eroticism and sexuality.', '"Sexuality,Enough,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Too often, older women are seen as victims, but I know lots of formidable women who have marvellous jobs as well as a full erotic life, and children and friends and family."', '"Life,Family,Women"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"When I was starting out, young actresses had the studio system to protect them. Now you have a host of sharks, from your agent to your publicist to your lawyer."', '"Lawyer,Sharks,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"You can love more than one person in your life, but things will be different. There\'ll be a different dynamic. Needs and desires change."', '"Life,Love,Change"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Each decade, I\'ve lived in that decade, so I could easily shed the \'20s, the \'30s, the \'40s."', '"Decade,Lived,Each"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I like working in theatre now and I think that once you\'ve done a certain amount of films most actors love working in the theatre because of the camaraderie.', '"Love,Done,Camaraderie"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"In films people basically work for the camera, you know, and that\'s why actors can hate each other and not be speaking to each other and still look as if they\'re in love because really they\'re loving the camera loving them."', '"Love,Work,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"My parents were hugely supportive like that. I was always the best - it\'s so embarrassing, isn\'t it? I was always the best at everything."', '"Best,Parents,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I don\'t think the media circus has ever been a shock to my life seeing as I was with Richard Burton and Elizabeth Taylor when I was 17.', '"Life,My Life,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I turned down a lot of films.', '"Down,Lot,Turned"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'After all my various relationships I find myself now home alone.', '"Alone,Home,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I have got a few misters interested but nobody special these days.', '"Nobody,Special,Days"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I was always going to be a dancer - I drifted into acting.', '"Acting,Always,Going"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I was seen dancing at school by a director, who asked me to be in a TV play. And it had a huge impact. So I think that\'s what really started me off."', '"Me,School,Impact"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'Fame and stardom sat very easily on Elizabeth Taylor\'s shoulders.', '"Fame,Shoulders,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Truly charismatic people, in my experience, don\'t come along very often."', '"Experience,People,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"You can be revered for all sorts of qualities, but to be truly charismatic is rare. Elizabeth Taylor was, for me, one of those rarities."', '"Me,Rare,Qualities"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"So many stars lose their way, and with success become more neurotic, not less so."', '"Success,Stars,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Everything is about class in England, whether it\'s upper, lower or middle. Why should that be?"', '"Everything,Why,Middle"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Everyone has class, one class or another."', '"Everyone,Class,Another"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'I never pursued being \'famous.\'', '"Famous,Never,Being Famous"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"Exposure makes you famous, not just good work. Famous is being plastered everywhere."', '"Work,Good,Famous"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"It\'s not so much the dressing up, but I love the idea of moving and existing in a different time."', '"Love,Time,Moving"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', 'An interview has become such a confrontational thing. It makes you very defensive.', '"Interview,Become,Defensive"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"From 1 till 7, when we moved to England, I spoke only Portuguese."', '"Only,England,Spoke"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"In the theatre, once you\'ve gone about eight rows back, everybody else is just listening to you. You\'re very small, and nobody can really see what you\'re doing."', '"Listening,Nobody,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I think you live a fuller life with someone else, you know, you\'re firing on all cylinders. It can be a nightmare at times, we all know that, but nevertheless in the end I think to have someone else\'s input on anything - a book, a meal, your children, life, a walk - is fantastic."', '"Life,Walk,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"My children were brought up with their grandparents, and I was brought up with my grandparents. I think the continuity of moving through life together gives people a certain pride and sense of security."', '"Life,Together,Pride"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"I\'ve never been too afraid of what other people have said, especially when I was younger, but I suppose that was the arrogance of youth."', '"Youth,Arrogance,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"The biggest privilege I\'ve had in my life is being able to make a choice. If you make a choice, it can\'t be a wrong choice because it seemed like a good idea at the time."', '"Life,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda5', '"My mother was madly adventurous. My father was an actor - he worked with Gielgud - and my mother came from a very wealthy family. She definitely wasn\'t meant to marry an actor, but she eloped with him one lunch-time."', '"Family,Father,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda9', '"Come dress yourself in love, let the journey begin."', '"Love,Journey,Dress"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda9', '"Search for beauty without features, something deeper than any signs."', '"Beauty,Search,Signs"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda9', 'I do suspect that this world is hell.', '"World,Hell,Suspect"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'Finding ways to unwind and switch off is just as important as working very hard.', '"Unwind,Important,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I recycle and try to reuse bags in shops but, like most people, I don\'t do as well as I could."', '"People,Try,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I feel like when you\'ve got a good outfit on it makes your day, right?"', '"Good,Day,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'m quite relaxed - I know it\'s important not to get too uptight about things as a dancer, but when it came to my voice I realised that everything you eat, everything you drink affects it."', '"Important,Voice,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'No one recognises me in the street.', '"Me,Street,Recognises"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'Everyone knows that I\'m not very nice when I\'m hungry.', '"Hungry,Everyone,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'You can\'t live your life with regrets about not doing something. It\'s so much better to just go for it.', '"Life,Better,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'ve loved CATS since I was a child - particularly the role of Victoria, so when the opportunity to audition came about I was very interested."', '"Opportunity,Cats,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'It\'s just very surreal for someone who doesn\'t sing in public to suddenly be singing with Jennifer Hudson.', '"Singing,Someone,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Obviously I would never have agreed to be a part of something that would change the colour of my skin had I been playing a human. The bottom line is, I\'m playing a cat. There is no more discussion. I am a cat that\'s white, let\'s not read into it."', '"Change,I Am,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I didn\'t expect to be so tired sometimes on stage. There are moments when you\'re so tired you could pretty much collapse.', '"Tired,Sometimes,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I just want always to move people at every performance. If someone cries, that\'s brilliant."', '"People,Performance,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I feel in control when I\'m on stage.', '"Feel,Control,Stage"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I\'d like to be remembered a little bit for my performances.', '"Remembered,Like,Little Bit"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'There was never really a moment that I decided that I wanted to be a ballet dancer. It\'s always just felt like it\'s what I was meant to do.', '"Moment,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"At aged eleven, you\'re learning taking criticism every day and making it a positive thing - otherwise you will never make it in ballet."', '"Positive,Learning,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I sew my own shoes - I don\'t trust anyone else to sew the ribbons exactly how I like them.', '"Trust,Shoes,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'When I\'m performing I just want to tell the audience something. I want every person watching to walk away feeling something.', '"Walk,Person,Watching"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I remember being asked for the first time about my race, and it really took me by surprise, just that it was a point that needed to be raised - and then I quickly realised that it was a point that everyone wanted to talk about!"', '"Time,Me,Surprise"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"My dad was teaching in Kenya, and my grandparents came to visit me there. They brought me to England, and my dad continued to teach for a bit after, so I just continued to live with my grandparents, because that became home, really."', '"Home,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I love acting, but that\'s also kind of what I love about ballet - the acting. So, obviously, film is like an extension of that, which is amazing, but it\'s also something I can do a bit later on as well."', '"Love,Amazing,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I feel that while my body\'s able and I\'m young, I\'d have so many regrets if I didn\'t go for it now with the ballet, because that\'s everything I\'ve always wanted to do."', '"Body,Feel,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"It\'s not a normal every day thing to see yourself with fur, but I loved it."', '"Yourself,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Telling the story from start to finish, that adrenaline fuels me and keeps me going."', '"Me,Start,Adrenaline"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I always critique myself but I\'m realistic - I know I can do better but I\'m never that hard on myself, either."', '"Myself,Better,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I already don\'t read reviews, I don\'t seek them out. Sometimes my family will tell me if there\'s a nice one."', '"Family,Me,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'Since the E.U. referendum I\'ve been keen to know more and be a bit more active. It highlighted how important politics is to our lives.', '"Politics,Important,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I would love to be a fashion designer but that\'s easier said than done.', '"Love,Done,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I believe that when we die, we die - but I believe people\'s energy stays behind."', '"Believe,Energy,Die"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'It took me a while to process myself as a cat - it\'s not something you see every day.', '"Myself,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Even in the early stages of my career I\'ve had to dance with principal dancers. I could have easily freaked out and got nervous, but I think that helped when it came to trying to forget I was doing a scene with Judi Dench."', '"Dance,Doing,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'m so happy that I ventured out beyond the Royal Ballet - which is my home, and I love it - but I would never have pushed myself outside of my comfort zone."', '"Love,Home,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"It sounds a cliche but when I\'m on stage I\'m at my most relaxed, I feel most like myself. When I have the music and the costumes and everyone else around me, that\'s when I feel most free."', '"Music,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I love to laugh as much as possible.', '"Love,Laugh,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'ve always just done ballet, and I feel like I\'m sort of living the dream."', '"Feel,Done,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I love all of the ballets that have a really strong story in them where I get to play a character. I don\'t enjoy the ones that are more technical without a story line and it\'s just me on stage dancing.', '"Love,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I had to learn about how to use my voice as an instrument, like a muscle in my body when I dance. I had no idea how much you could do with your voice and how much you have to look after it."', '"Look,Body,Dance"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"For a long time everyone had a stereotype of ballet that it was easy and that we were just prancing around. But thanks to the Internet, and being able to share live performances and broadcast them to the world so that everyone can experience the ballet, I think it\'s inspiring people we wouldn\'t normally be able to reach."', '"Experience,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"For people who know about dance, \'Cats\' is a musical that really celebrates dance, and there are so many different styles of dance in this film, too. I was really looking forward to being part of that."', '"Looking Forward,Looking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Manon\' still feels like it didn\'t really happen, because it is such a mammoth ballet and I can\'t believe I did that."', '"Believe,Because,Happen"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I definitely have been nervous, but often I get more nervous performing with the corps de ballet than doing a solo. There\'s so much pressure doing a group number because if you muck it up, you\'ve ruined it for everyone."', '"Pressure,Doing,Group"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I always enjoy ballet when you can read the situation very precisely, when I could tell you exactly which sentence that person is saying to that person even when they\'re not speaking and just moving their hand."', '"Situation,Person,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"With Juliet, if you read the Shake\'speare there is quite a clear idea of how she should be, but with the ballet you can get your teeth into her even more because there are loads of moments when you realise she is growing up."', '"Teeth,Your,She"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I was a waitress at a local pub. I was really bad with money and it taught me the value of it as I was on minimum wage.', '"Money,Me,Value"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I learned after a while that you are the only one who can take care of yourself.', '"Yourself,Care,Take Care"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I\'m rubbish at maths but I would like to have been a pilot.', '"Pilot,Like,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'m very proud of the colour of my skin and that I\'m inspiring people from all backgrounds, but I think it will be great for the next mixed-race or black female principal dancer if she doesn\'t have to be asked about that."', '"Great,Black,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"In ballet, it doesn\'t matter who you are. If you\'re good, it\'s such a rare thing, so unusual, that the talent will go wherever you want it to go."', '"Good,Talent,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"When I was younger, in my living room, I used to put \'Cats\' the stage musical video on and I used to copy Victoria."', '"Living Room,Living,Copy"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'When I was younger I used to dance to lots of ballet videos.', '"Dance,Videos,Younger"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"On stage I have to amplify some of my emotions with my back or make something a little bit more obvious because my audience might be very far away from me, or very high up and find it harder to read what I\'m trying to express."', '"Me,Emotions,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"When I found out that I was going be Juliet, it felt much more real than \'Manon,\' because \'Manon\' is one of those ballets that you probably do after Juliet, so that never really sunk in to be honest."', '"Real,Never,More"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'The force for change I represent is of course from being a mixed-race ballerina.', '"Change,Force,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"When I was a wee baby, if I heard any music, I would just get up in my buggy or my pram and start bobbing around."', '"Music,Start,Baby"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"It\'s very British of me, but I\'ll always choose beer over anything else."', '"Me,Beer,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I got the performance gene.', '"Performance,Got,Gene"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Sometimes I wonder if people really want my smelly old shoes, but some people seem quite thrilled by them. So I\'m like, OK, well, this is something you can\'t buy, so there you go."', '"Shoes,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"My favorite leisurewear brands are Lululemon and Nike. They feel like a second skin, they never restrict my movements, and they keep me cool and warm."', '"Cool,Me,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"Dancewear is very different from sportswear. Sportswear doesn\'t quite suit what we need to do with our bodies, so I\'m always fiddling with my clothes in the studio."', '"Always,Clothes,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I don\'t like wearing frilly, puffy skirts."', '"Like,Skirts,Puffy"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I love fashion. It\'s actually - after ballet - my favourite thing since I was little.', '"Love,Fashion,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'ve always been distracted by shopping and when I\'m not dancing, I\'m probably shopping."', '"Shopping,Always,Distracted"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I have so many clothes, but really, I have the same variations of the same thing, usually black jeans, black jumpers, black double-breasted coats."', '"Black,Clothes,Jeans"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'My friends and family would not let me get big-headed - they make sure I stay grounded.', '"Family,Me,Friends And Family"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I\'ve had to learn not be freaked out by big roles... and to take it all one step at a time, quite literally."', '"Time,Step,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', 'I\'d definitely like to do some more film acting.', '"Acting,More,Film"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"I am embarrassed to say that I regularly wake up to a message from my Matchesfashion.com personal shopper, saying, \'Hey, it\'s Charlene, just letting you know about this handbag before everyone else!\'"', '"I Am,Wake Up,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda6', '"As a dancer, I am either in something glamorous or I am rocking up to work in a leotard and my pyjamas. Dressing in between is quite difficult."', '"Work,I Am,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"Writing is very cathartic for me. As a teacher, I hear many students say that writing can be painful and exhausting. It can be, but ultimately I believe that if you push through, the process is healing and exhilarating."', '"Teacher,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"I think depression creates in me an urgent need to write, but I also believe that daily stress, and even the positive \'stress\' of intense happiness, can compel me to express myself through the written word."', '"Positive,Happiness,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"I love Sylvia Plath and Anne Sexton. I also love more cerebral poets like H.D. and Emily Dickinson. My parents subscribed to a monthly poetry periodical, and as a teenager I was introduced to Denise Levertov, who was an influence."', '"Love,Poetry,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"It\'s scary to become a woman in this world. We have to understand that some of the messages we get, messages that we are not enough, are there to keep our power in check. We can\'t buy into these messages."', '"Power,World,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"Writing is literally transformative. When we read, we are changed. When we write, we are changed. It\'s neurological. To me, this is a kind of magic."', '"Me,Magic,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', '"I am constantly thinking ahead to what I want to write about in the future, and when I\'m done with one project, I give myself a little time and then start the next one."', '"Future,Time,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda7', 'Write with abandon and no constraints for first draft. Cut brutally and save in separate files on second draft. Add conflict; don\'t be afraid to make your characters suffer. Read what you love. Write what you love. Love.', '"Love,Conflict,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda8', '"When I met Dante I didn\'t work in the movies, but I enjoyed so much the movies. I worked in interior design and when I met Dante, we tried to do something together."', '"Work,Movies,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fda8', '"There is no difficult moment working together because when we start a new project, Dante starts to make all the sketches and I can see the vision of the movie and then I start my job."', '"Moment,Vision,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaa', 'I always saw photography as a way to get to film.', '"Way,Always,Photography"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaa', 'I\'m not interested in just beautiful girls and beautiful clothes.', '"Beautiful,Not Interested,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaa', '"I\'m more interested in photographing people who have done something, like writers or directors - even billionaires - as long as I can study them before I photograph them."', '"Long,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaa', '"To me, the main and most exciting thing about photography is to meet people. The picture is the result of what happened between me and them on the set."', '"Me,Result,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"Since there is nothing so well worth having as friends, never lose a chance to make them."', '"Friendship,Chance,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'The return we reap from generous actions is not always evident.', '"Brainy,Always,Reap"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"I know no man who feels deeper disgust than I do at the ambition, avarice, and profligacy of the priesthood, as well because every one of these vices is odious in itself, as because each of them separately and all of them together are utterly abhorrent in men making profession of a life dedicated to God."', '"Life,God,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'Let no one trust so entirely to natural prudence as to persuade himself that it will suffice to guide him without help from experience.', '"Trust,Experience,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"The affairs of this world are so shifting and depend on so many accidents, that it is hard to form any judgment concerning the future; nay, we see from experience that the forecasts even of the wise almost always turn out false."', '"Future,Experience,Wise"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'Waste no time with revolutions that do not remove the causes of your complaints but simply change the faces of those in charge.', '"Change,Time,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'Affairs that depend on many rarely succeed.', '"Succeed,Depend,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'One who imitates what is bad always goes beyond his model; while one who imitates what is good always comes up short of it.', '"Good,Bad,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'There is nothing so fleeting as the memory of benefits received.', '"Memory,Nothing,Fleeting"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"Few revolutions succeed, and when they do, you often discover they did not gain what you hoped for, and you condemn yourself to perpetual fear, as the parties you defeated may always regain power and work for your ruin."', '"Work,Power,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"Conspiracies, since they cannot be engaged in without the fellowship of others, are for that reason most perilous; for as most men are either fools or knaves, we run excessive risk in making such folk our companions."', '"Men,Fellowship,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"Pay no heed to those who tell you that they have relinquished place and power of their own accord, and from their love of quiet. For almost always they have been brought to this retirement by their insufficiency and against their will."', '"Love,Power,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"Like other men, I have sought honours and preferment, and often have obtained them beyond my wishes or hopes. Yet never have I found in them that content which I had figured beforehand in my mind. A strong reason, if we well consider it, why we should disencumber ourselves of vain desires."', '"Men,Mind,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"If you attempt certain things at the right time, they are easy to accomplish - in fact, they almost get done by themselves. If you undertake them before the time is right, not only will they fail, but they will often become impossible to accomplish even when the time would have been right."', '"Time,Impossible,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', '"It is a great matter to be in authority over others; for authority, if it be rightly used, will make you feared beyond your actual resources."', '"Great,Will,Matter"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdab', 'Ambition is not in itself an evil; nor is he to be condemned whose spirit prompts him to seek fame by worthy and honourable ways.', '"Ambition,Spirit,Evil"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', '"I was born into a profession in which my love of words, chosen with care for their meaning and nuance, was extremely important, not only to me, but also to the people with whom I worked with."', '"Love,Me,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', 'I\'ve lived an amazing life. There\'s no reason to focus on the bad. They teach you that in racing school. Keep your eye where you want your front tire to be. You don\'t want to be stuck in the rut? Then don\'t look at the rut. Always look at where you want to go.', '"Life,Amazing,Focus"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', 'There are two kinds of people on this Earth: Those who are content and those who are not.', '"People,Earth,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', '"I could be winning the decathlon in high school, which I\'ve won twice, yet, if my dad is in the audience, \'Oh look! It\'s Anthony Quinn.\' And I\'m like, \'Hello? Kid just got a gold medal. Hello? I\'m over here.\'"', '"Dad,Look,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', '"What I\'d like to pass on to my children is the thirst for knowledge. It\'s something I experience every day that I learned from my father. He always taught me that no matter how long you\'ve done something, you can always learn something new and be better at what you do."', '"Knowledge,Experience,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdac', '"I learned from an early age that my heritage, my love for people, and my desire to be a vehicle that can be used through my voice, that my expressions and actions can transport a person to experience a scene from the past, present and future."', '"Love,Future,Experience"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"Football, to me, is a passion, more than a game. It is everything. But more than anything, it is love for Roma. I have always been Roma. There has never been anything else."', '"Love,Football,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"Winning one league title at Roma, to me, is worth winning 10 at Juventus or Real Madrid."', '"Me,Winning,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"I never thought about money; otherwise, I would have left aged 26 when Real Madrid and Barcelona wanted me."', '"Money,Me,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"I was born Roman, and I\'ll die Roman. I\'ll never leave this team or my city."', '"City,Die,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"When you grow up, you gain experience and realise what youre capable of."', '"Experience,Grow,Gain"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"To the children of yesterday, who have grown up and become parents, and to the children of today, who perhaps shout \'Tottigol,\' I\'d like to think that, for you, my career has become a fairytale for you to pass on."', '"Today,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'There aren\'t many athletes who follow their hearts. They choose to go somewhere to win more and earn more money. They\'re like gypsies.', '"Money,Win,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"During a game, it comes down to your mind - the pressure. There are loads of other aspects, too. Many people say taking penalties is easy, but when you\'re stood over one, that\'s not the case. It\'s in no way easy. The goal really does become a lot smaller."', '"Mind,Game,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"The game has given me so much, and I tried to give so much back to the people who have showed me so much love day after day."', '"Love,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'Being born Roman and Romanisti is a privilege.', '"Born,Privilege,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'The Santiago Bernabeu is an amazing stadium.', '"Amazing,Stadium"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'I would tell the young Francesco Totti to repeat everything that the older Totti did - if he\'s able to!', '"Young,Everything,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"The first part of my life, as a player, has ended but now I\'m heading into an equally important part as a manager, hoping to do as well as I did on the field."', '"Life,My Life,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'I am fortunate to have only worn one shirt in my career. It is something that is fundamental to me. It is something I have always wanted: to be one of these few who wear only one shirt - a fan and a player of the same team.', '"Me,I Am,Shirt"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"When I do retire, I will miss the trips with the team, the jokes with my teammates, the habits: having breakfast with them, playing with them, all the little things."', '"Breakfast,Little Things,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"I am not thinking about life after football, but I know it will be another life, another world."', '"Life,Football,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"Playing further up the pitch, you have more opportunities to score and provide assists, and it\'s something I liked right from the start."', '"Start,Right,More"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"I find it easier to strike the ball with my instep across goal. But I\'ve scored in loads of other ways, too."', '"Find,Ball,Strike"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"Before being a player, I was a diehard fan of Roma, so I know what the fans felt when we won."', '"Fans,Know,Fan"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', 'Roma come before everything else.', '"Everything,Come,Before"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"Over the years, I\'ve tried to express myself through my feet, which have made everything simpler for me ever since I was a child."', '"Myself,Me,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdad', '"The end of my playing career was May 28, 2017. That, for me, was an historic day. I\'ll carry it with me forever. It will be hard to explain to people the feelings and emotions I felt that day."', '"Me,Day,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'It took me years to realize that \'normal\' is actually super boring and that being myself was harder but infinitely more rewarding.', '"Myself,Me,Being Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Social media, unfortunately, just makes it a lot easier to be jealous. It sets up false expectations of reality, so it\'s really easy to look at someone else\'s life online and assume that they have everything going great for them and that their life is perfect."', '"Life,Great,Reality"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"The Internet is a blessing and a curse. I mean, it\'s a place where lots of people can express themselves, which is amazing, but it\'s a place where a lot of people can express themselves that probably should keep those expressions to themselves."', '"Amazing,Internet,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'What I love most about SZA\'s music is her unflinching vulnerability.', '"Love,Music,Vulnerability"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Self-care is really about taking care of you and focusing on feeling good about yourself - mind and body.', '"Good,Mind,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For whatever reason, illiteracy continues to plague the racist troll community."', '"Community,Whatever,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m very self-deprecating, so I\'m not afraid to make jokes at my own expense, and I\'ve just found that makes people a little more comfortable and can open the door for people to feel a little bit more understanding and accepting of where you\'re coming from."', '"Feel,Door,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"If you\'re brave enough to search \'Franchesca Ramsey\' on YouTube, you\'ll find a sea of ranting white dudes pinning the \'angry black woman\' stereotype onto my smiling face."', '"Black,Angry,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I think, even before social media, it was really hard to not look at other classmates and say, \'Well I wish I looked like her.\' Or even to look at celebrities and wish that \'I looked like them.\'"', '"Look,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"My undergrad degree was in graphic design, and I don\'t work in that anymore, but I obviously do a lot of design and editing and Photoshopping, and the Adobe Creative Cloud is essential!"', '"Work,Design,Editing"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Now I have a standard for how I make sure people do not speak to me in a way that I feel uncomfortable with. When I was younger, I didn\'t have that. I was like, \'Try not to make waves.\' I wanted everybody to like me, and so I stifled a lot of the discomfort that I had."', '"Me,Way,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Castor oil has long been a used as a remedy for a whole host of ailments including arthritis, digestion, insomnia and even period cramps. But it also stimulates hair growth."', '"Growth,Long,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'The main problem with cultural appropriation comes from dominant groups \'borrowing\' from marginalized groups who face oppression or have been stigmatized for their cultural practices throughout history.', '"History,Face,Oppression"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"People feel really uncomfortable talking about race and identity, largely because the subject is so taboo."', '"Feel,People,Uncomfortable"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Self-esteem doesn\'t have to just be about the way you look; it can be about your talents and passions. All of those things can build someone\'s confidence and show them that they have self worth and they are important.', '"Confidence,Look,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"As much as we try to deny it, media plays a huge part in how we view the world."', '"View,World,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"It\'s just not funny to disrespect other people\'s beliefs, backgrounds, cultures, or identities when those are deeply rooted in longstanding oppression. Jokes that punch down on marginalized people require no creativity because they\'ve existed since the beginning of time. It\'s like telling a knock-knock joke and believing you\'re Richard Pryor."', '"Funny,Time,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"In many ways, being yourself is dispelling stereotypes."', '"Yourself,Stereotypes,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"What\'s really great about social media is we have tremendous access, and there\'s a wealth of information about the people that we admire online."', '"Great,Social Media,Information"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I believe there\'s a huge conflict of interest when local prosecutors investigate cases of police violence within their own communities.', '"Police,Believe,Conflict"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'The Internet is an actual dumpster fire.', '"Fire,Internet,Actual"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'ve had lots of people say, \'Oh, Franchesca\'s content is just for white people.\' But I try to talk about identity in a way that\'s accessible to lots of people and is not a pointed finger."', '"Way,People,White"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'We can\'t all wake up and know everything.', '"Wake Up,Know,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'The Internet has been so good to me; I see its potential to help other people.', '"Good,Me,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Growing up, I was constantly labeled an \'oreo\' by my black peers because of my proper speech and \'valley girl accent.\'"', '"Black,Valley,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Over the years, I\'ve found that dealing with white people faux pas can be tricky. If I get upset, I could quickly be labeled the \'angry black girl.\' But if I don\'t say anything or react too passively, I risk giving friends and acquaintances permission to continue crossing the line."', '"Black,Angry,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m obsessed with cute gym clothes in bright bold prints, so as soon as Mara Hoffman expanded into activewear, I knew my wallet was in danger."', '"Cute,Bold,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Sounds cliched, but I can\'t survive without my calendar."', '"Survive,Calendar,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"My debut book is a collection of personal stories and advice about communication on the Internet. More specifically, the downfall of communication because of the Internet."', '"Communication,Internet,Advice"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Social media isn\'t as quaint as it was when I started my Livejournal back in high school.', '"Social Media,Media,School"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For me, social media isn\'t just about connecting with friends and sharing photos; it\'s a bigger, more tangled web that\'s led me to jobs working in television, speaking gigs around the country, and it\'s even helped me land my first book deal!"', '"Me,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'The truth is that the performative nature of social media can turn even the simplest conversations into a WWE style cage match with emojis and Internet slang taking the place of pratfalls and over the top costumes.', '"Nature,Truth,Social Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I love Uniqlo for all the staples, but what I really love are the palazzo pants. They are just so flattering."', '"Love,Pants,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I have really long legs, so I like cropped pants that make it look like I intentionally wanted my pants short instead of pants that happen to be too short for me."', '"Look,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I love my journal as much as I love my phone. I find it to be a big part of my self-care to reflect on my day and write words that inspire me or paste business cards and pictures.', '"Love,Business,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"\'Stop playing the victim.\' - unless you\'ve been cast in a community theater production of \'Law & Order: SVU,\' I\'m not sure why anyone would choose to play victim."', '"Community,Law,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Just as you\'re allowed to be angry about injustice, it\'s natural to express feelings of sadness or fear, especially if you\'re exhausted by the prospect of trying to keep a brave face."', '"Fear,Angry,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"People feel like using the word \'joke\' removes responsibility for the hurt their words may cause. It doesn\'t; in fact, it may make things worse."', '"Responsibility,Words,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"When I get to meet my audience when I go speak at colleges or when I\'m walking down the street, it\'s been really eye-opening how many people have been touched to see someone that looks like them on television."', '"Street,Walking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I think what\'s been really awesome about the Internet is the ability to reach people from so many different walks of life and stages in their life.', '"Life,Internet,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For a black activist, for an activist of all walks of life, the Internet has become this kind of meeting place where we can exchange ideas, where we can learn from each other, where we can get inspired about new ways that we can make changes within our own communities and own homes."', '"Life,Black,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I\'m so inspired by people like Issa Rae who started on YouTube or Abbi and Ilana from \'Broad City\' who also started on YouTube.', '"City,YouTube,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Whether you have locs, natural hair, wear a relaxer, or rock wigs and weaves, thinning edges can be a frustrating issue."', '"Hair,Rock,Wear"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m embarrassed to admit that I thought the world was ending my junior year of high school after a dye job reacted badly with my perm and left me with a sparse and burnt up hairline. Even though I went natural a few years later, my edges never seemed to recover."', '"Me,World,Ending"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'It\'s important to understand you can\'t remove the historical context of racially charged stereotypes or slurs as much as we like to pretend that we can.', '"Important,Stereotypes,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Becoming a police officer is a choice. It\'s not something you\'re born into.', '"Police,Choice,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For content creators, it\'s really important to be honest. Your audience will appreciate if you\'re stingy with the brands you work with."', '"Work,Important,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'My hair videos are usually styling videos answering people\'s questions about natural hair.', '"Hair,People,Questions"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'My channel is an opportunity to give people a new perspective on natural hair. Love what you have and work with what you\'ve got. I think that\'s really important.', '"Love,Work,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"The Internet is part of my job, so I have to approach it with a level of professionalism. I don\'t necessarily think it\'s changed who I am, but if anything, it\'s impacted the opportunities that have come into my life and the people that I\'ve been able to develop relationships with - which I\'m very fortunate and thankful for."', '"Life,Thankful,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For me, YouTube was about creating content because I had an interest in beauty and comedy and wanted to find a way to mix those two things, and I could do it from my home, own my own time."', '"Beauty,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Beauty is really cool because it\'s something that can make you feel good about yourself.', '"Beauty,Cool,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I always make sure to moisturize my hair. I love natural oils, coconut oil. Moisture is one thing you can never go wrong with."', '"Love,Hair,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'The biggest thing I try to do is to unplug and give myself time away from social media and the Internet.', '"Time,Myself,Social Media"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I was looking for help with styling my hair and was really struggling to find it, and I have very much been of the mind that if you see a need for something, and you can create it yourself, then go for it, so I started creating content around beauty."', '"Beauty,Mind,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"You create content because you love it, not necessarily because you\'re looking for fame or know what it will potentially lead to."', '"Love,Looking,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m just really excited to expose people to different identities, different conversations but also to kind of reframe how they think about black women just by being myself."', '"Women,Myself,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'There are some white people who are very unhappy that I am in an interracial relationship.', '"Relationship,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m, like, not a science person at all."', '"Science,Person,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"There was a long stretch of time where I was making these videos, and everyone just thought I was a weirdo because I was making videos in my apartment instead of, like, going out, you know. And so I, like, it\'s hilarious now because everyone gets YouTube now. But, you know, in 2006, when I started making videos, like, no."', '"Time,Long,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For me, like, my goal has never been, quote, unquote, \'mainstream success.\' I\'ve just always wanted to work in entertainment."', '"Success,Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'You have to realize that people are always going to be confused or sometimes threatened by someone who has the confidence to do something different.', '"Confidence,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I think that\'s the thing I love about making content online - you get instant response.', '"Love,Online,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Women really love their hair. Like, our hair is very important."', '"Love,Women,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Everyone\'s journey is their own journey. Everyone gets to where they are supposed to be. Everyone\'s journey works out the way they\'re supposed to.', '"Journey,Way,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Oftentimes people say to me, \'Oh I didn\'t know you could do so much with locs until I saw your videos or I saw photos of you at events.\' So whenever I hear that people have been really inspired to experiment with their hair or their look because of me, it\'s very flattering and really cool."', '"Cool,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I like to think my work is furthering black culture by educating and empowering black people.', '"Work,Black,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"My ultimate goal is to make people laugh and make them think, which isn\'t always an easy task."', '"People,Laugh,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Black people come in so many different bodies, genders, and sexualities, so it\'s important that we\'re conscious of that so we can fight for a world that embraces and uplifts black people of every kind. Our voices are powerful and have the ability to make change."', '"Change,Black,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"It\'s important to take time away from the Internet as much as possible. For me, I love working out, and my husband and I do it together in the mornings! And it\'s really our time to check in with each other, but it\'s also our time to really not think about work or what\'s happening on the Internet."', '"Love,Work,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I think society perpetuates a lot of mixed messages about what it means to be beautiful for all women, but especially for black women and women of color."', '"Women,Society,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'YouTube is an amazing platform to talk about social issues because it gives people the ability to tell their own stories and reach audience around the world who may otherwise never be exposed to these people and conversations.', '"Amazing,World,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Black women are so very often stereotyped in pop culture.', '"Women,Black,Culture"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'Black women come with all sorts of personalities. So it\'s time for media to wise up and show us in all of our complexity.', '"Women,Time,Black"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"With \'Decoded,\' the goal is to just keep pushing forward and challenging ourselves to tackle important subjects in creative and funny ways."', '"Funny,Important,Creative"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I\'m somewhat wary of being called \'woke\' because it feels absolute in a way that I don\'t think is realistic.', '"Way,Because,Realistic"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"My consciousness is a process, and that includes my relationship with my husband. His being white doesn\'t make me any less black or invested in black issues, the same way him being a man doesn\'t make me any less of a feminist."', '"Relationship,Black,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"For me, at least with my parents, I feel that they wanted me to have all the opportunities that they did not have, and for them, that meant going to private school."', '"Me,Parents,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I think the beauty of the Internet is that it\'s giving a lot of people the opportunity to reach people around the world that they never would have been able to, and for people to tell their own stories where they don\'t see themselves reflected in mainstream media, or the media is misrepresenting the truth, right."', '"Beauty,Truth,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I create videos for my YouTube channel Chescaleigh and for \'Decoded,\' a series with MTV."', '"YouTube,Create,Videos"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I left acting school really hoping that I could be on a television show of some sort, working in movies in Hollywood."', '"Movies,School,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"When I started in 2007, YouTube was just a fun hobby for others and myself."', '"Myself,Fun,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'My dream has always been to be in entertainment.', '"Entertainment,Always,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"In reality, there are tons of unrepresented voices that we don\'t see in comedy."', '"Reality,Comedy,See"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Unfortunately, oftentimes people hire and give opportunities to people that look like them. They don\'t realize how much their own internal lives or privilege gets in the way of looking for people outside of the traditional spaces where they always find people."', '"Look,Looking,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '\'Decoded\' is definitely close to my heart.', '"Heart,Close,Definitely"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"If I know you, and you want to touch my hair, you should ask me first, and most of the time I\'ll say yes. But if I don\'t know you, and you just reach out and touch me without asking or touch while simultaneously asking, I\'m going to give you a side eye."', '"Time,Me,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I can recall an instance where I was in a meeting at work giving a presentation in front of my board of directors. I was taking questions at the end and someone asks, \'Is that your hair real?\' The man then reached out and started stroking my hair. It was completely bizarre to me."', '"Work,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I have been talking about social issues on YouTube for a long time now. I think it\'s very important in terms of being able to reach people around the world and people who have never been exposed to certain topics or are maybe misinformed about certain things.', '"Time,World,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I initially started making videos about my hair because I was struggling to style it and didn\'t know where to find help. Similarly, I started creating comedy content and doing characters and talking about things that were important to me because I didn\'t find a place to do that in the career that I wanted as an actress."', '"Me,Style,Hair"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I think doing research is probably the most valuable thing you can do for any career you\'re interested in pursuing, and not just a career on YouTube or in media. Really take a look at people whose careers you admire and learning from their successes, but also their mistakes."', '"Learning,Look,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I enjoy working out because I struggle with anxiety, and exercise has been a great way for me to combat that."', '"Great,Struggle,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"\'Lemonade\' resonated with me, and I love the direction Beyonce is going with her music and her career."', '"Love,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I don\'t want to tell anybody who to vote for; I\'d rather people just do their homework and make sure they vote for the person that they feel like is best to run our country.', '"Best,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"Do not feed the trolls! Racist commenters usually troll the Internet looking for people of color to harass online. If you avoid responding, oftentimes they will get bored and move on."', '"Internet,Looking,People"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"People that are not happy in their offline life tend to turn to trolling to fill the void. Oftentimes, the people saying racist things do not even necessarily believe in what they are saying. They are just looking for attention they do not get in real life. When you keep that in mind, it is easier to avoid indulging those people all together."', '"Life,Together,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I think that the most important thing when it comes to achieving your dreams is just that you have to be realistic.', '"Dreams,Your Dreams,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', 'I think that everyone on the Internet has to deal with people saying negative things. It can be tough!', '"Internet,Negative,Tough"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I think that if you stay positive and remain positive, you can definitely achieve the things you set out to."', '"Positive,Achieve,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdae', '"I\'m very fortunate to have a husband and friends and family that are super supportive of my career in all aspects. I do so many different things, it\'s really nice to have a support network that includes him and my parents and my friends that encourage me to continue to work towards whatever it is that I want to do."', '"Work,Family,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"I really like Neutrogena for skin care and CoverGirl makeup. I can\'t stand heavy makeup. I feel like my skin can\'t breathe, and CoverGirl is really light."', '"Light,Skin,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"I like to carry a concealer palette that has a green, a yellow, and a tan color. I like to carry the green one because when I have a pimple, it\'s good to use that to contrast the red. Then you put the yellow over it, and it helps it disappear."', '"Good,Green,Red"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"It was hard at school because, growing up, some people wanted to be friends with me just because they wanted to get to my dad and say that they had met him and had gone to our house. I didn\'t understand it at the time, but the older I got and the more aware of it I became, it started becoming hard."', '"Time,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', 'I\'m glad I went through all the normal teenage dramas that a lot of people go through. I can really relate to \'Secret Life\' because I witnessed those similar struggles.', '"Life,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"I was a dancer when I got discovered, and I started working immediately. I started being in commercials and doing guest star roles. My first big thing, which happened maybe six months after being discovered, was \'Bring It On: All or Nothing.\'"', '"Nothing,Doing,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"I still have a lot of my friends from high school. You just know who is there for you for real, and who is trying to get something out of you."', '"School,Real,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"My eyelashes are divas, so they will like a mascara brand one week or for a month, and then they\'ll just stop working for it. I go back and forth between Maybelline and Cover Girl, and then I carry around a primer, too."', '"Will,Back,Stop"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"I love Clinique. Their moisturizer is amazing. My skin tends to be really oily, but then at times I\'m dry, and that\'s the perfect amount of moisturizer."', '"Love,Amazing,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"Even though I\'m Hispanic, I\'m so white."', '"White,Even,Though"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdaf', '"Find a type of exercise that you love - whether it\'s dance, soccer, softball, anything - just as long as it keeps you active. If you love it, you\'ll dedicate yourself to it and stay involved."', '"Love,Yourself,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb0', 'I was outraged to learn that the president wanted to outsource operations at some American ports to the United Arab Emirates.', '"American,Operations,President"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb0', '"It\'s the No.1 issue with people I talk to, whether Republican, Democrat or independent. They want to see the way business is done in Washington change."', '"Change,Business,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb0', '"Like you, I\'m fed up with business as usual in Washington. Send me to Congress, and I won\'t tweak our broken system. I\'ll shut it down."', '"Business,Me,Broken"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb0', 'This is not about being liberal. This is not about being conservative. This is about making sure our government works for all Americans.', '"Government,Conservative,About"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"No matter when you were born or where, puberty is the same. It\'s the same for your parents as it is for you - what\'s happening in your body dictates everything."', '"Parents,Body,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"When I first thought of the idea for \'Sweet Valley High,\' I loved the idea of high school as microcosm of the real world. And what I really liked was how it moved things on from \'Sleeping Beauty\'-esque romance novels where the girl had to wait for the hero. This would be girl-driven, very different, I decided - and indeed it is."', '"Sweet,Hero,World"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"I always loved reading. Growing up, my favorite book was \'A Child\'s Garden of Verses,\' by Robert Louis Stevenson."', '"Always,Garden,Loved"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"I get some of my ideas from watching my three daughters, but most of them come from my own memories of growing up. I can remember how romantic I was, not just about love, but romance in the classic sense - the romantic ideals: of honor and truth, of loyalty, sacrifice and fairness. Those were the elements that made a story satisfying to me."', '"Love,Truth,Romantic"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', 'I always had a fascination with twins.', '"Always,Twins,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"Since I was a small child, I was always writing either poems or plays... plays in which I had the starring part."', '"Always,Small,Child"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"I know you think that when you\'re 35, 45, 55, you\'ll be different. But I\'m going to let you in on a bit of a secret. You\'re going to look different, and your life is going to be different, but in your head you\'ll always be that 16-year-old girl."', '"Life,Look,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', 'I like to play poker. I have a nice poker group that\'s been going on for years.', '"Group,Nice,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', 'I don\'t do rewrites. I put all the pages in a pile next to the typewriter.', '"Next,Typewriter,Pile"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb1', '"The same way that some people can play the piano, I can do plots! They just come!"', '"Way,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'Fact-checking is so boring compared to writing fiction.', '"Boring,Writing,Fiction"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"\'One Hundred Years of Solitude\' convinced me to drop out of Harvard graduate school. The novel reminded me of everything my Ph.D. program was trying to make me forget. Thank you, Gabriel Garcia Marquez."', '"Me,Solitude,School"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"If things are going well I can easily spend twelve hours a day writing, but not writing writing, just thinking and revising and taking a comma out and putting it back in."', '"Thinking,Day,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"For any writer, the ability to look at a sentence and see what\'s superfluous, what can be altered, revised, expanded, and, especially, cut, is essential. It\'s satisfying to see that sentence shrink, snap into place, and ultimately emerge in a more polished form: clear, economical, sharp."', '"Look,See,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'I work really long days and I work seven day weeks.', '"Work,Long,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"I know a lot of Eastern Europeans, and because of what they have been through and what they have seen, they have an attitude where they are not easily fooled."', '"Attitude,Know,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'I went through college in the 1960s without having any idea that I was going to have to make a living. When I graduated in 1968 it was quite a shock to find out that there was a world out there and that it wasn\'t going to support me.', '"Me,World,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"Of course, I\'ve always read. I started when I was four years old and just didn\'t stop. I read all the time."', '"Time,Always,Stop"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'I wrote about four novels before I wrote a word of journalism.', '"Journalism,Four,About"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"I think poets are much more dramatic, more theatrical than fiction writers."', '"More,Dramatic,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"A lot of girls who turn into something remarkable start off as irrepressible, confident and a handful."', '"Start,Turn,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'I\'m in a rage all of the time.', '"Time,Rage"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', 'I think of myself as someone with a kind of Tourette\'s. I cannot help saying the thing you\'re not supposed to say.', '"Myself,Help,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"Long before the idea of a writer\'s conference was a glimmer in anyone\'s eye, writers learned by reading the work of their predecessors. They studied meter with Ovid, plot construction with Homer, comedy with Aristophanes; they honed their prose style by absorbing the lucid sentences of Montaigne and Samuel Johnson."', '"Work,Long,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"A work of art can start you thinking about some aesthetic or philosophical problem; it can suggest some new method, some fresh approach to fiction."', '"Work,Art,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"I remember, when I was a little kid, I was good at sports, and I could jump off the high board. And then puberty hit, and suddenly I was looking to boys for direction. I remember that as a great loss."', '"Good,Great,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb2', '"I can no more reread my own books than I can watch old home movies or look at snapshots of myself as a child. I wind up sitting on the floor, paralyzed by grief and nostalgia."', '"Home,Movies,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"My favorite book is \'Redeeming Love.\' It was my first as a born-again Christian, my statement of faith, and the most exciting year I\'ve spent writing anything."', '"Love,Faith,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"I had been raised in the church, but I wasn\'t a Christian. I had a lot of head knowledge but no heart knowledge."', '"Knowledge,Heart,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', 'I want to see Christian fiction speak to the hard and real issues that tear people\'s lives apart.', '"People,Real,See"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"Well, I always wanted to write from the time I was very little, and my mother encouraged me. She wrote a journal from the time she was 15 up until about the age of 76."', '"Time,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"I start work by spending time in personal Bible study. Because my projects center on a question in my own faith walk, I find Bible study essential. And God gives me scriptures daily that speak to the question with which I\'m struggling."', '"Work,Faith,God"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"Like everyone else, there are days when I don\'t want to go to work. However, writing is a job like anything else."', '"Work,Anything,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', 'I\'ll often dream about characters before I start writing their stories.', '"Start,Writing,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', 'The goal is to have every character take on a life of his or her own. Sometimes characters will come into the story that I haven\'t planned.', '"Life,Character,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"That is one of the reasons I write: to feel the Presence of God and know He is speaking to me in a very personal way, instructing me, correcting me, redirecting me."', '"God,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', 'My job is to allow the character to live and breathe - and become as real to the reader as he or she is to me.', '"Character,Me,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"When we love like Jesus does, lives change for the better."', '"Love,Change,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"I became a Christian late, in my late 30s, so I had a lot of things that I was bringing into my Christian life that I regret. And I had a lot of questions about faith, so that\'s where I start when I write."', '"Life,Faith,Regret"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb3', '"I actually worked in the general market for many years writing steamy historical romance, and I had more freedom in the Christian market than I ever did in the general market to write about any issue that I needed to write about."', '"Freedom,More,Historical"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', '"In the eye of the tornado, there\'s no more high and low, no floor and sky."', '"Sky,More,Eye"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', 'I have no problem twisting the facts if it\'s the only way I can be true to the moment.', '"Moment,Facts,True"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', '"We\'ve lost control of this planet somewhere. There\'s an echo in that kind of tornado situation, where you\'re powerless facing those phenomena."', '"Lost,Control,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', '"What I can\'t tell with a photo I will tell with a painting, and what I can\'t tell with a painting I will tell with a video or text sometimes, et cetera."', '"Painting,Sometimes,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', 'Can that make any sense - a Belgian artist living in Mexico and working in Afghanistan?', '"Living,Artist,Mexico"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', '"Formulating the proposal is about 80% of the actual time of the process. In the end, the time spent filming, editing and postproduction is a very small proportion of the total time you spend in the production of the film."', '"Time,Editing,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', '"I am interested in seeing how a certain situation can develop with potential accidents. First, I am inspired by the acts of potential collaborators. It tends to be an action they have already done in a different context. I am very clear about the rules of the game, but once it\'s launched, I don\'t intervene at all."', '"Game,Action,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb4', 'I am always fascinated by the way kids create their own world. That is something I am very attentive to anywhere I go.', '"World,I Am,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', 'Vatican II declares the Church... as necessary for salvation.', '"Church,Salvation,Necessary"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"Religion is one dimension of culture, a transcendent element of it."', '"Religion,Culture,Element"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"Remarkable is the greater openness of the Catholic Church towards people of other religious traditions and persuasions. The development has not been without problems, since some people have resisted it and others have pushed openness beyond the desirable point."', '"Problems,People,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"With reference to other religions, the Church sees a great difference between them and herself. The other religions are expressions of the human soul seeking God, with some beautiful spiritual insights, but also not without errors. Christianity is rather God seeking humanity."', '"God,Great,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"There is no dogma that the organ or harmonium can be used in church, but not the drum."', '"Church,Drum,Dogma"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"The Catholic faith never changes. But the language and mode of manifesting this one faith can change according to peoples, times and places."', '"Change,Faith,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', '"Even among the married, sexual satisfaction must not be sought in a way which disregards man\'s character as a person and degrades him to the animal level."', '"Character,Man,Satisfaction"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb5', 'There is a tendency around the world today to copy TV culture. And that is not always a virtue.', '"Today,Culture,World"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb6', '"We should so work as if we were to be saved by our works; and so rely on Jesus Christ, as if we did no works."', '"Work,Jesus Christ,Did"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb6', 'My soul is more at rest from the tempter when I am busily employed.', '"Soul,I Am,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb7', '"Affliction is a school of virtue; it corrects levity, and interrupts the confidence of sinning."', '"Confidence,School,Virtue"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb7', '"They who are not induced to believe and live as they ought by those discoveries which God hath made in Scriptures would stand out against any evidence whatever, even that of a messenger sent express from the other world."', '"God,Believe,World"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb7', '"The greater absurdities are, the more strongly they evince the falsity of that supposition from whence they flow."', '"More,Flow,Greater"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb8', 'With a group of bankers I always had the feeling that success was measured by the extent one gave nothing away.', '"Success,Nothing,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb8', 'The male sex still constitute in many ways the most obstinate vested interest one can find.', '"Sex,Find,Interest"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Reading maketh a full man; conference a ready man; and writing an exact man.', '"Man,Ready,Writing"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Beauty itself is but the sensible image of the Infinite.', '"Beauty,Image,Sensible"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"In order for the light to shine so brightly, the darkness must be present."', '"Light,Darkness,Shine"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'It is impossible to love and to be wise.', '"Love,Wisdom,Wise"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'There is no excellent beauty that hath not some strangeness in the proportion.', '"Beauty,Proportion,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Truth is the daughter of time, not of authority."', '"Truth,Time,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Knowledge is power.', '"Knowledge,Power,Knowledge Is Power"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The best part of beauty is that which no picture can express.', '"Beauty,Best,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"He that hath wife and children hath given hostages to fortune; for they are impediments to great enterprises, either of virtue or mischief."', '"Great,Wife,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Fortitude is the marshal of thought, the armor of the will, and the fort of reason."', '"Strength,Will,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:51:00', '2023-05-29 11:51:00'),
	('395569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The remedy is worse than the disease.', '"Disease,Worse,Remedy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Nature, to be commanded, must be obeyed."', '"Nature,Must,Obeyed"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'What is truth? said jesting Pilate; and would not stay for an answer.', '"Truth,Answer,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Wives are young men\'s mistresses, companions for middle age, and old men\'s nurses."', '"Women,Age,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Revenge is a kind of wild justice, which the more a man\'s nature runs to, the more ought law to weed it out."', '"Nature,Revenge,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Men fear death as children fear to go in the dark; and as that natural fear in children is increased by tales, so is the other."', '"Death,Men,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Hope is a good breakfast, but it is a bad supper."', '"Hope,Good,Breakfast"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Natural abilities are like natural plants, that need pruning by study; and studies themselves do give forth directions too much at large, except they be bounded in by experience."', '"Experience,Plants,Too Much"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"A little philosophy inclineth man\'s mind to atheism, but depth in philosophy bringeth men\'s minds about to religion."', '"Men,Religion,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Imagination was given to man to compensate him for what he is not; a sense of humor to console him for what he is.', '"Humor,Imagination,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"I will never be an old man. To me, old age is always 15 years older than I am."', '"Age,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Travel, in the younger sort, is a part of education; in the elder, a part of experience."', '"Education,Experience,Travel"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'A wise man will make more opportunities than he finds.', '"Wise,Man,Wise Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"God Almighty first planted a garden. And indeed, it is the purest of human pleasures."', '"God,Gardening,Garden"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Age appears to be best in four things; old wood best to burn, old wine to drink, old friends to trust, and old authors to read."', '"Best,Trust,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"If a man\'s wit be wandering, let him study the mathematics."', '"Education,Man,Mathematics"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Certainly, in taking revenge, a man is but even with his enemy, but in passing it over, he is superior; for it is a prince\'s part to pardon."', '"Revenge,Man,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'A man that studieth revenge keeps his own wounds green.', '"Anger,Revenge,Green"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The job of the artist is always to deepen the mystery.', '"Art,Mystery,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Silence is the sleep that nourishes wisdom.', '"Wisdom,Silence,Sleep"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Opportunity makes a thief.', '"Opportunity,Thief,Makes"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"If a man will begin with certainties, he shall end in doubts, but if he will content to begin with doubts, he shall end in certainties."', '"Man,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Houses are built to live in, and not to look on: therefore let use be preferred before uniformity."', '"Look,Live,Use"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Some books are to be tasted, others to be swallowed, and some few to be chewed and digested."', '"Others,Few,Books"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"A bachelor\'s life is a fine breakfast, a flat lunch, and a miserable dinner."', '"Life,Breakfast,Lunch"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'There is no comparison between that which is lost by not succeeding and that which is lost by not trying.', '"Lost,Trying,Comparison"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Silence is the virtue of fools.', '"Silence,Virtue,Fools"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"If we do not maintain justice, justice will not maintain us."', '"Justice,Will,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'We cannot command Nature except by obeying her.', '"Nature,Cannot,Her"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Young people are fitter to invent than to judge; fitter for execution than for counsel; and more fit for new projects than for settled business.', '"Business,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"It is as natural to die as to be born; and to a little infant, perhaps, the one is as painful as the other."', '"Die,Born,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"It is a strange desire, to seek power, and to lose liberty; or to seek power over others, and to lose power over a man\'s self."', '"Power,Man,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Prosperity is not without many fears and distastes; adversity not without many comforts and hopes.', '"Fear,Adversity,Prosperity"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Money is like manure, of very little use except it be spread."', '"Money,Use,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Who questions much, shall learn much, and retain much."', '"Questions,Who,Learn"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"In taking revenge, a man is but even with his enemy; but in passing it over, he is superior."', '"Revenge,Man,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Whosoever is delighted in solitude is either a wild beast or a god.', '"God,Solitude,Beast"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Things alter for the worse spontaneously, if they be not altered for the better designedly."', '"Change,Better,Worse"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Truth emerges more readily from error than from confusion.', '"Truth,Confusion,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"They are ill discoverers that think there is no land, when they can see nothing but sea."', '"Imagination,Sea,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The great end of life is not knowledge but action.', '"Life,Knowledge,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Acorns were good until bread was found.', '"Good,Bread,Found"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"But men must know, that in this theatre of man\'s life it is reserved only for God and angels to be lookers on."', '"Life,God,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Studies serve for delight, for ornaments, and for ability."', '"Ability,Delight,Serve"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'He that will not apply new remedies must expect new evils; for time is the greatest innovator.', '"Change,Time,New"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Read not to contradict and confute, nor to believe and take for granted... but to weigh and consider."', '"Believe,Take For Granted,Take"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"The root of all superstition is that men observe when a thing hits, but not when it misses."', '"Men,Superstition,Observe"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"He that gives good advice, builds with one hand; he that gives good counsel and example, builds with both; but he that gives good admonition and bad example, builds with one hand and pulls down with the other."', '"Good,Advice,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Fashion is only the attempt to realize art in living forms and social intercourse.', '"Art,Living,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Wise men make more opportunities than they find.', '"Wisdom,Men,Wise"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Friends are thieves of time.', '"Time,Thieves,Friends"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Prosperity is the blessing of the Old Testament; adversity is the blessing of the New.', '"Adversity,New,Blessing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Nature is often hidden, sometimes overcome, seldom extinguished."', '"Nature,Sometimes,Hidden"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Discretion of speech is more than eloquence, and to speak agreeably to him with whom we deal is more than to speak in good words, or in good order."', '"Good,Words,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Children sweeten labours, but they make misfortunes more bitter."', '"Children,More,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"If a man be gracious and courteous to strangers, it shows he is a citizen of the world."', '"Man,World,Strangers"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'A prudent question is one-half of wisdom.', '"Wisdom,Question,Prudent"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Anger makes dull men witty, but it keeps them poor."', '"Men,Anger,Poor"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"The genius, wit, and the spirit of a nation are discovered by their proverbs."', '"Genius,Spirit,Nation"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Science is but an image of the truth.', '"Science,Truth,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"The joys of parents are secret, and so are their grieves and fears."', '"Parents,Secret,Fears"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Fortune is like the market, where, many times, if you can stay a little, the price will fall."', '"Will,Fall,Fortune"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Seek ye first the good things of the mind, and the rest will either be supplied or its loss will not be felt."', '"Good,Mind,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The place of justice is a hallowed place.', '"Justice,Place,Hallowed"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'There is a difference between happiness and wisdom: he that thinks himself the happiest man is really so; but he that thinks himself the wisest is generally the greatest fool.', '"Happiness,Wisdom,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"There is nothing makes a man suspect much, more than to know little."', '"Man,Nothing,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"God\'s first creature, which was light."', '"God,Light,First"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Write down the thoughts of the moment. Those that come unsought for are commonly the most valuable.', '"Moment,Thoughts,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"It is in life as it is in ways, the shortest way is commonly the foulest, and surely the fairer way is not much about."', '"Life,Way,About"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'God hangs the greatest weights upon the smallest wires.', '"God,Greatest,Wires"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Who ever is out of patience is out of possession of their soul.', '"Patience,Soul,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Knowledge and human power are synonymous.', '"Knowledge,Power,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The worst men often give the best advice.', '"Best,Men,Advice"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The worst solitude is to have no real friendships.', '"Solitude,Real,Worst"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"This is certain, that a man that studieth revenge keeps his wounds green, which otherwise would heal and do well."', '"Revenge,Green,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Truth is so hard to tell, it sometimes needs fiction to make it plausible."', '"Truth,Sometimes,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Rebellions of the belly are the worst.', '"Worst,Belly"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Fame is like a river, that beareth up things light and swollen, and drowns things weighty and solid."', '"River,Light,Fame"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Friendship increases in visiting friends, but in visiting them seldom."', '"Friendship,Friends,Visiting"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"The way of fortune is like the milkyway in the sky; which is a number of small stars, not seen asunder, but giving light together: so it is a number of little and scarce discerned virtues, or rather faculties and customs, that make men fortunate."', '"Men,Sky,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Virtue is like a rich stone, best plain set."', '"Best,Rich,Stone"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"I do not believe that any man fears to be dead, but only the stroke of death."', '"Death,Man,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Small amounts of philosophy lead to atheism, but larger amounts bring us back to God."', '"God,Back,Small"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'A sudden bold and unexpected question doth many times surprise a man and lay him open.', '"Man,Surprise,Unexpected"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Choose the life that is most useful, and habit will make it the most agreeable."', '"Life,Habit,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The subtlety of nature is greater many times over than the subtlety of the senses and understanding.', '"Nature,Understanding,Senses"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'There is a wisdom in this beyond the rules of physic: a man\'s own observation what he finds good of and what he finds hurt of is the best physic to preserve health.', '"Wisdom,Best,Health"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Nothing doth more hurt in a state than that cunning men pass for wise.', '"Men,Wise,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'It is natural to die as to be born.', '"Die,Born,Natural"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'By indignities men come to dignities.', '"Men,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The momentous thing in human life is the art of winning the soul to good or evil.', '"Life,Good,Art"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'People have discovered that they can fool the devil; but they can\'t fool the neighbors.', '"Devil,Fool,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"I had rather believe all the Fables in the Legend, and the Talmud, and the Alcoran, than that this universal frame is without a Mind."', '"Believe,Mind,Legend"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Life, an age to the miserable, and a moment to the happy."', '"Life,Age,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"As the births of living creatures are at first ill-shapen, so are all innovations, which are the births of time."', '"Time,Living,Creatures"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"There is as much difference between the counsel that a friend giveth, and that a man giveth himself, as there is between the counsel of a friend and of a flatterer. For there is no such flatterer as is a man\'s self."', '"Man,Self,Difference"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The desire of excessive power caused the angels to fall; the desire of knowledge caused men to fall.', '"Knowledge,Men,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The fortune which nobody sees makes a person happy and unenvied.', '"Nobody,Person,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"People usually think according to their inclinations, speak according to their learning and ingrained opinions, but generally act according to custom."', '"Learning,People,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"It is a true rule that love is ever rewarded, either with the reciproque or with an inward and secret contempt."', '"Love,Love Is,True"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Judges must beware of hard constructions and strained inferences, for there is no worse torture than that of laws."', '"Torture,Hard,Judges"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Nothing is pleasant that is not spiced with variety.', '"Nothing,Pleasant,Variety"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Certainly the best works, and of greatest merit for the public, have proceeded from the unmarried, or childless men."', '"Best,Men,Merit"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Therefore if a man look sharply and attentively, he shall see Fortune; for though she be blind, yet she is not invisible."', '"Man,Look,See"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Studies perfect nature and are perfected still by experience.', '"Nature,Experience,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Truth is a good dog; but always beware of barking too close to the heels of an error, lest you get your brains kicked out."', '"Truth,Good,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Lies are sufficient to breed opinion, and opinion brings on substance."', '"Opinion,Lies,Substance"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The quarrels and divisions about religion were evils unknown to the heathen. The reason was because the religion of the heathen consisted rather in rites and ceremonies than in any constant belief.', '"Religion,Belief,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The pencil of the Holy Ghost hath labored more in describing the afflictions of Job than the felicities of Solomon.', '"Pencil,Job,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Antiquities are history defaced, or some remnants of history which have casually escaped the shipwreck of time."', '"History,Time,Shipwreck"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Anger is certainly a kind of baseness, as it appears well in the weakness of those subjects in whom it reigns: children, women, old folks, sick folks."', '"Women,Anger,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"We are much beholden to Machiavel and others, that write what men do, and not what they ought to do."', '"Men,Others,Much"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'Pictures and shapes are but secondary objects and please or displease only in the memory.', '"Memory,Only,Objects"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Riches are a good hand maiden, but a poor mistress."', '"Good,Poor,Mistress"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'They that will not apply new remedies must expect new evils.', '"New,Will,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Judges ought to be more leaned than witty, more reverent than plausible, and more advised than confident. Above all things, integrity is their portion and proper virtue."', '"Integrity,Judges,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"A man must make his opportunity, as oft as find it."', '"Opportunity,Man,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Many a man\'s strength is in opposition, and when he faileth, he grows out of use."', '"Strength,Man,Opposition"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Of all virtues and dignities of the mind, goodness is the greatest, being the character of the Deity; and without it, man is a busy, mischievous, wretched thing."', '"Busy,Character,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"For my name and memory I leave to men\'s charitable speeches, and to foreign nations and the next ages."', '"Men,Memory,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'He that hath knowledge spareth his words.', '"Knowledge,Words,He"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"No body can be healthful without exercise, neither natural body nor politic, and certainly, to a kingdom or estate, a just and honourable war is the true exercise."', '"War,Exercise,True"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'The correlative to loving our neighbors as ourselves is hating ourselves as we hate our neighbors.', '"Hate,Neighbors,Loving"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'When a man laughs at his troubles he loses a great many friends. They never forgive the loss of their prerogative.', '"Great,Man,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Good fame is like fire; when you have kindled you may easily preserve it; but if you extinguish it, you will not easily kindle it again."', '"Good,Fire,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"God has placed no limits to the exercise of the intellect he has given us, on this side of the grave."', '"God,Intelligence,Exercise"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', '"Next to religion, let your care be to promote justice."', '"Religion,Justice,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdb9', 'It is as hard and severe a thing to be a true politician as to be truly moral.', '"True,Politician,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"Faith without works is like a bird without wings; though she may hop with her companions on earth, yet she will never fly with them to heaven."', '"Faith,Bird,Fly"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'Kiss till the cow comes home.', '"Home,Cow,Kiss"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"Oh, love will make a dog howl in rhyme."', '"Love,Will,Dog"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'Nothing\'s so dainty sweet as lovely melancholy.', '"Sweet,Nothing,Melancholy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'There is a method in man\'s wickedness; it grows up by degrees.', '"Man,Up,Wickedness"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"Envy, like the worm, never runs but to the fairest fruit; like a cunning bloodhound, it singles out the fattest deer in the flock."', '"Fruit,Envy,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'You are no better than you should be.', '"Better,Than,Should"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"The true way to gain much, is never to desire to gain too much."', '"True,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'It is more noble by silence to avoid an injury than by argument to overcome it.', '"Silence,Argument,Overcome"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"Let no man fear to die, we love to sleep all, and death is but the sounder sleep."', '"Love,Death,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', '"Interest makes some people blind, and others quick-sighted."', '"People,Blind,Some People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'Bad\'s the best of us.', '"Best,Bad,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdba', 'But what is past my help is past my care.', '"Past,Care,Help"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbb', 'The Constitution has not greatly bothered any wartime President.', '"Constitution,President,Bothered"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbb', '"I\'m for catching every Japanese in America, Alaska, and Hawai\'i now and putting them in concentration camps."', '"America,Now,Alaska"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbc', 'Although I had arrived in total darkness the light of truth at once burst upon my mind and I perceived most clearly that the republicans had overreached themselves.', '"Truth,Light,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbc', 'Do you think Revolutions are made with rose water?', '"Water,Rose,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbc', 'If you dispute with me you will only quarrel with your bread and butter.', '"Me,Will,Bread"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbd', '"One lifetime is never enough to accomplish one\'s horticultural goals. If a garden is a site for the imagination, how can we be very far from the beginning?"', '"Gardening,Imagination,Goals"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbd', 'Gardeners instinctively know that flowers and plants are a continuum and that the wheel of garden history will always be coming full circle.', '"History,Circle,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbe', '"Unfortunately, I never knew my father and when I did, it was very briefly."', '"Father,Never,Did"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbe', '"I think that even though my father wasn\'t there, in his death and in his memory, he has been a mentor to me in my manhood because my mom couldn\'t teach me how to be a man."', '"Death,Mom,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Truth is, I think, if God just gave us our daily bread, many of us would be angry. \'That\'s all you\'re going to give me? You\'re just going to give me enough to sustain me for today? What about tomorrow or next year or 10, 20, 30 years from now? I want to know that I\'m set up.\' And yet Jesus says just pray for your daily provisions."', '"God,Truth,Today"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"When I read the statements of Christ, there seems to be this urgency and intensity. I guess that\'s what I get out of it when I read the tone of the Scriptures, which is very different from the tone of our culture."', '"Culture,Urgency,Guess"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"If you really want to experience God, go and make disciples."', '"God,Experience,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'Our culture is all about shallow relationships. But that doesn\'t mean we should stop looking each other in the eye and having deep conversations.', '"Culture,Looking,Stop"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Honestly, when I read the Scriptures, I really believe the Lord puts a heart in us when we become believers."', '"Heart,Believe,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"I want to help people understand how to study the Scriptures with other people, to give them an overview of Scripture and assume that by understanding the Scriptures better, the Holy Spirit will bring to mind the right stories, the right teachings."', '"Mind,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"As a culture, we\'re so worried about what\'s going to happen to us 30 years from now that we are not taking care of our brothers and sisters who need help today."', '"Today,Culture,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'I\'ve never felt a need to really respond to someone else\'s writing.', '"Never,Someone,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"There are just certain times I sense the Lord is wanting me to write, and so I write."', '"Me,Lord,Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"It\'s easy to write for God and about God, because what a thrill to remind the church that the Holy Spirit of God is in you. What a rush! What an amazing blessing!"', '"God,Amazing,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"There are periods that we forget that in the pursuit of fruit, that if we just abide in Him, then fruitfulness is a guarantee."', '"Fruit,Forget,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"For a person to be truly discipled and growing in their faith, they need more than one person discipling them."', '"Faith,Person,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"A key to everything is surrender - to really come before the Lord and say, \'I will literally stay here as long as you want me to stay\' or \'God, I will really go anywhere on the earth.\'"', '"God,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"I want the joy of knowing that I am doing something with my life, the joy of battle."', '"Life,Battle,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'One of my biggest fears - maybe my biggest weakness as a Christian - is that I have a hard time going up to a stranger and talking to them about Jesus.', '"Time,Stranger,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Every year in my life, I trust fewer and fewer people."', '"Life,Trust,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Due to our consumer mindset, people are prone to jump from church to church, which weakens the church overall."', '"People,Church,Jump"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"When you read the New Testament, you see the Holy Spirit was supposed to change everything so that this gathering of people who call themselves Christians had this supernatural element about them."', '"Change,New,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Being around a church culture, even leading a gathering of believers, I\'ve gotten pretty good at predicting what\'s going to happen in a church service."', '"Good,Culture,Service"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'Our God listens to us. Our God is a living God. He\'s not a block of wood you made up that\'s not going to answer you. My God listens to me. He answers me.', '"God,Me,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"When I don\'t think biblically, I go nuts. I just go, \'This is crazy.\'"', '"Crazy,Go,Nuts"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Even in my own church I heard the words, \'Francis Chan\' more than I heard the words, \'Holy Spirit.\'"', '"Words,Spirit,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'Churches we build only by our own efforts and not in the strength of the Spirit will quickly collapse when we don\'t push and prod people along.', '"Strength,People,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"Churchgoers in America are notorious for jumping into movements, even ideas that are hard to listen to. But when they actually have to change their lifestyle and do something about it, it rarely translates into action."', '"Change,Action,America"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"I could fill my whole time doing interviews, speaking to crowds, and there\'s this natural human tendency because of our culture to think that the more people I talk to, the bigger the impact I\'ll have, and yet Jesus didn\'t spend His time just speaking to the masses. He spent the bulk of his time with a small group of people."', '"Time,Culture,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'Parents are supposed to instruct their kids. It doesn\'t mean they necessarily have that gift of teaching.', '"Gift,Parents,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"If I have a script, I tend to stick to it even if God may be leading me elsewhere in the moment."', '"God,Moment,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', '"With my natural communication abilities, I could probably gather a crowd even without the Spirit."', '"Communication,Spirit,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdbf', 'I could be wrong about salvation. I could be wrong about a lot of things.', '"Wrong,Salvation,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"The brain is the most complicated organ in the universe. We have learned a lot about other human organs. We know how the heart pumps and how the kidney does what it does. To a certain degree, we have read the letters of the human genome. But the brain has 100 billion neurons. Each one of those has about 10,000 connections."', '"Heart,Brain,Universe"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I became an atheist because, as a graduate student studying quantum physics, life seemed to be reducible to second-order differential equations. Mathematics, chemistry and physics had it all. And I didn\'t see any need to go beyond that."', '"Life,Mathematics,Atheist"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I believe God did intend, in giving us intelligence, to give us the opportunity to investigate and appreciate the wonders of His creation. He is not threatened by our scientific adventures."', '"God,Intelligence,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'When does life begin? When does the soul enter? That\'s a religious question. Science is not going to be able to help with that.', '"Life,Science,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"God gave us free will, and we may choose to exercise it in ways that end up hurting other people."', '"God,Free,Exercise"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Research is so unpredictable. There are periods when nothing works and all your experiments are a disaster and all your hypotheses are wrong.', '"Research,Nothing,Disaster"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Nobody gets argued all the way into becoming a believer on the sheer basis of logic and reason. That requires a leap of faith.', '"Faith,Way,Logic"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'One must dig deeply into opposing points of view in order to know whether your own position remains defensible. Iron sharpens iron.', '"View,Know,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"Faith is reason plus revelation, and the revelation part requires one to think with the spirit as well as with the mind. You have to hear the music, not just read the notes on the page."', '"Faith,Music,Mind"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I\'m a serious Christian. I take my faith seriously. I try to practice it every day of the week, not just on Sunday."', '"Faith,Day,Practice"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I actually do not believe that there are any collisions between what I believe as a Christian, and what I know and have learned about as a scientist. I think there\'s a broad perception that that\'s the case, and that\'s what scares many scientists away from a serious consideration of faith."', '"Faith,Believe,Perception"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"As a Christian, but also as a scientist responsible for overseeing the Human Genome Project, one of my concerns has been the limits on applications of our understanding of the genome. Should there be limits? I think there should. I think the public has expressed their concern about ways this information might be misused."', '"Limits,Information,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"For me, in my Christian belief, prayer is not an opportunity to manipulate God into doing what you want him to. Prayer is an opportunity to have a conversation with God to try to get in tune with what his will is."', '"God,Prayer,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"If I\'m walking down the riverbank, and a man is drowning, even if I don\'t know how to swim very well, I feel this urge that the right thing to do is to try to save that person. Evolution would tell me exactly the opposite: preserve your DNA. Who cares about the guy who\'s drowning?"', '"Man,Me,The Right Thing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I\'m enormously interested to see where neuroscience can take us in understanding these complexities of the human brain and how it works, but I do think there may be limits in terms of what science can tell us about what does good and evil mean anyway, and what are those concepts about?"', '"Science,Good,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Many people struggle with losing weight and then regaining it. But there is no convincing evidence that the effort to lose weight actually promotes more weight gain in the long run.', '"Struggle,Lose,Effort"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'God is an awesome mathematician and physicist.', '"God,Awesome,Physicist"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'So much of what we are currently seeing as far as human suffering and misery comes from diseases that should have been preventable but were not.', '"Suffering,Seeing,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Patenting tends to get people\'s juices flowing when you put the word \'gene\' and the word \'patent\' in the same sentence. And understandably so. This is stuff we\'re carrying around - all of us - inside all of our cells. Should somebody be able to lay claim to it?', '"People,Inside,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"A cardinal principle that we must not stray from - no exceptions - is that your genetic information is your business in terms of who sees it. Nobody should be gaining access to that information without your explicit permission, and nobody should be requiring you to take a genetic test unless you decide that that\'s what you want to do."', '"Business,Information,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"Science\'s domain is the natural. If you want to understand the natural world and be sure you\'re not misleading yourself, science is the way to do it."', '"Science,World,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Successful weight management really means a permanent change in lifestyle - and success in this arena provides that person with a great opportunity to model that behavior for friends and family.', '"Success,Change,Family"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I believe in the literal rising of the body of Christ. It\'s the cornerstone of my Christian faith.', '"Faith,Believe,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I trained initially as a physical chemist, and then, after becoming interested in biology, I went to medical school and learned how to be a physician. So, I\'m a physician scientist."', '"Medical,Biology,School"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"A virus is not just DNA; a virus is also packaged up, covered over with a series of proteins in a nice, elegant, well-compacted form."', '"DNA,Nice,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I\'m a pretty informal guy. I ride a Harley.', '"Ride,Pretty,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"The shelves of many evangelicals are full of books that point out the flaws in evolution, discuss it only as a theory, and almost imply that there\'s a conspiracy here to avoid the fact that evolution is actually flawed. All of those books, unfortunately, are based upon conclusions that no reasonable biologist would now accept."', '"Flaws,Accept,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"People who are in a position of finding out that they\'re at risk for some illness, whether it\'s breast cancer, or heart disease, are afraid to get that information - even though it might be useful to them - because of fears that they\'ll lose their health insurance or their job."', '"Health,Heart,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I think history would say that medical research has, throughout many changes of parties, remained as one of the shining lights of bipartisan agreement, that people are concerned about health for themselves, for their families, for their constituents."', '"Health,History,Medical"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I think there are people who\'s lives have been saved because of the study of the genome.', '"People,Because,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"The best diet is the one that can be sustained over the long term, combined with other healthful lifestyle behaviors."', '"Best,Diet,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"For delightfully quirky descriptions of bizarre neurological syndromes that teach us a lot about how the brain works, there is no match for Oliver Sacks."', '"Brain,Us,Match"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I finished up my graduate degree in quantum mechanics, but underwent a bit of a personal crisis, recognizing that I didn\'t want to do that for the rest of my life. It was too abstract, too far removed from human concerns."', '"Life,My Life,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"Growing up, I was vaguely aware of things that went on in church, because I was in the boys\' choir at the local Episcopal church. But I got the clear message that I was supposed to learn music there, and not pay too much attention to the rest of it, and I followed those instructions very carefully."', '"Music,Rest,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"As a scientist, you\'re not supposed to make decisions without the data."', '"Data,Without,Decisions"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"My own area of expertise is the genetics of human disease. I was fortunate to be part of the team that found the genes for cystic fibrosis, and Huntington\'s disease and neurofibromatosis."', '"My Own,Own,Genes"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"If God is real, and I believe he is, then he is outside of nature. He is, therefore, not limited by the laws of nature in the way that we are."', '"Nature,God,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I\'m always feeling like I\'m lacking wisdom. This reassurance that one can ask God for that and it will happen is certainly reassuring to me.', '"Wisdom,God,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I\'ve never heard God speak out loud to me. That\'s not an experience I have had.', '"God,Experience,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'We give our kids vaccinations. That\'s a biological enhancement that\'s considered not just acceptable but actually admirable.', '"Just,Kids,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"If you are looking for a needle in a haystack, and somebody has already cataloged all the straw in the haystack, when you get to that needle you will recognize it\'s different than what was supposed to be there based on all that computerized haystack information that had been predetermined for you."', '"Information,Looking,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I don\'t have a problem with the concept that miracles might occasionally occur at moments of great significance, where there is a message being transmitted to us by God Almighty. But as a scientist, I set my standards for miracles very high."', '"God,Great,Miracles"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"In my own experience as a physician, I have not seen a miraculous healing, and I don\'t expect to see one."', '"Experience,See,Healing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'What faith has not been used by demagogues as a club over somebody\'s head?', '"Faith,Club,Head"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"Genes are effectively one-dimensional. If you write down the sequence of A, C, G and T, that\'s kind of what you need to know about that gene. But proteins are three-dimensional. They have to be because we are three-dimensional, and we\'re made of those proteins. Otherwise we\'d all sort of be linear, unimaginably weird creatures."', '"Weird,Know,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"Cancer is a disease of the genome. And that\'s what happens. You make mistakes in a cell somewhere in your body that causes it to start to grow when it should\'ve stopped, and that\'s cancer. And those mistakes are mistakes of DNA."', '"Grow,Body,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'A technological advance of a major sort almost always is overestimated in the short run for its consequences - and underestimated in the long run.', '"Long,Always,Consequences"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"I\'m aware there are certain products that are being advertised - food products - with \'no chemicals whatsoever.\' Well, that would be pretty hard to arrange, since everything around us is made up of atoms and molecules - chemicals - including ourselves."', '"Food,Everything,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'The word \'living\' has so many connotations that I\'m almost reluctant to try to define it scientifically because it sounds as if I\'m then downgrading all the other significances of that word.', '"Living,Try,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Sometimes you develop a passion for something because of some personal experience.', '"Experience,Passion,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'I took care of young adults with cystic fibrosis when I was in my residency training and found this to be a disease that was desperately in need of some explanation.', '"Training,Care,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Proponents of intelligent design don\'t accept that some of the very complex nanomachines that we have inside ourselves could have come about solely on the basis of natural selection.', '"Design,Accept,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"If you are in support of in vitro fertilization, then you have to recognize that human embryos are being created in excess of what can be used safely to reimplant for a pregnancy. So they\'re going to end up being discarded."', '"Support,End,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', '"It is interesting that the U.S. has this very strong proportion of the population that rejects scientific conclusions about the age of the Earth and about evolutionary relationships between species, including humans."', '"Age,Earth,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'It\'s interesting when you read the life of Christ how much of his time he spent healing the sick. There must have been a reason for that - he was modelling for us what it is we are intended to do by following his path.', '"Life,Time,Path"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc0', 'Scientists must venture outside their comfort zones to show the public how cool - and how important - their work really is.', '"Cool,Work,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"It is one of the more striking generalizations of biochemistry - which surprisingly is hardly ever mentioned in the biochemical textbooks - that the twenty amino acids and the four bases, are, with minor reservations, the same throughout Nature."', '"Nature,More,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'We\'ve discovered the secret of life.', '"Life,Secret,The Secret Of"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"Attempts have been made from a study of the changes produced by mutation to obtain the relative order of the bases within various triplets, but my own view is that these are premature until there is more extensive and more reliable data on the composition of the triplets."', '"View,Data,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'Unfortunately it makes the unambiguous determination of triplets by these methods much more difficult than would be the case if there were only one triplet for each amino acid.', '"Determination,Difficult,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"It would appear that the number of nonsense triplets is rather low, since we only occasionally come across them. However this conclusion is less secure than our other deductions about the general nature of the genetic code."', '"Nature,Nonsense,Low"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"It now seems very likely that many of the 64 triplets, possibly most of them, may code one amino acid or another, and that in general several distinct triplets may code one amino acid."', '"Now,Acid,Code"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"Moreover the incorporation requires the same components needed for protein synthesis, and is inhibited by the same inhibitors. Thus the system is most unlikely to be a complete artefact and is very probably closely related to genuine protein synthesis."', '"Genuine,Protein,System"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"The meaning of this observation is unclear, but it raises the unfortunate possibility of ambiguous triplets; that is, triplets which may code more than one amino acid. However one would certainly expect such triplets to be in a minority."', '"Observation,Meaning,Minority"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'We are sometimes asked what the result would be if we put four +\'s in one gene. To answer this my colleagues have recently put together not merely four but six +\'s.', '"Together,Colleagues,Result"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"This seems highly likely, especially as it has been shown that in several systems mutations affecting the same amino acid are extremely near together on the genetic map."', '"Together,Map,Acid"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"It seems likely that most if not all the genetic information in any organism is carried by nucleic acid - usually by DNA, although certain small viruses use RNA as their genetic material."', '"Information,DNA,Small"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'It now seems certain that the amino acid sequence of any protein is determined by the sequence of bases in some region of a particular nucleic acid molecule.', '"Protein,Now,Acid"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"It has yet to be shown by direct biochemical methods, as opposed to the indirect genetic evidence mentioned earlier, that the code is indeed a triplet code."', '"Indeed,Code,Evidence"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"If, for example, all the codons are triplets, then in addition to the correct reading of the message, there are two incorrect readings which we shall obtain if we do not start the grouping into sets of three at the right place."', '"Start,Place,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"If the code does indeed have some logical foundation then it is legitimate to consider all the evidence, both good and bad, in any attempt to deduce it."', '"Good,Foundation,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"If poly A is added to poly U, to form a double or triple helix, the combination is inactive."', '"Combination,Double,Triple"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"The balance of evidence both from the cell-free system and from the study of mutation, suggests that this does not occur at random, and that triplets coding the same amino acid may well be rather similar."', '"Random,Balance,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"How is the base sequence, divided into codons? There is nothing in the backbone of the nucleic acid, which is perfectly regular, to show us how to group the bases into codons."', '"Nothing,Group,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'For simplicity one can think of the + class as having one extra base at some point or other in the genetic message and the - class as having one too few.', '"Simplicity,Point,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', '"Do codons overlap? In other words, as we read along the genetic message do we find a base which is a member of two or more codons? It now seems fairly certain that codons do not overlap."', '"Words,Find,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'A final proof of our ideas can only be obtained by detailed studies on the alterations produced in the amino acid sequence of a protein by mutations of the type discussed here.', '"Ideas,Protein,Acid"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc1', 'A comparison between the triplets tentatively deduced by these methods with the changes in amino acid sequence produced by mutation shows a fair measure of agreement.', '"Measure,Comparison,Acid"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc2', '"In science, the credit goes to the man who convinces the world, not to whom the idea first occurs."', '"Science,Man,World"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc2', 'There seems to be one quality of mind which seems to be of special and extreme advantage in leading him to make discoveries. It was the power of never letting exceptions go unnoticed.', '"Power,Mind,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc3', '"There must be a beginning of any great matter, but the continuing unto the end until it be thoroughly finished yields the true glory."', '"Great,True,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I think cinema, movies, and magic have always been closely associated. The very earliest people who made film were magicians."', '"Movies,Cinema,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"The essence of cinema is editing. It\'s the combination of what can be extraordinary images of people during emotional moments, or images in a general sense, put together in a kind of alchemy."', '"Together,Editing,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"We had access to too much money, too much equipment, and little by little, we went insane."', '"Money,Too Much,Equipment"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I don\'t think there\'s any artist of any value who doesn\'t doubt what they\'re doing.', '"Art,Value,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I like simplicity; I don\'t need luxury.', '"Simplicity,Luxury,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was raised as a Catholic, but I didn\'t like the Catholic Church at all. I thought the nuns were mean."', '"Church,Mean,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"We were raised in an Italian-American household, although we didn\'t speak Italian in the house. We were very proud of being Italian, and had Italian music, ate Italian food."', '"Food,Music,Italian Food"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was always the black sheep of the family and always told that I was dumb, and I had a low IQ and did badly in school."', '"Family,Black,Dumb"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I think it\'s better to be overly ambitious and fail than to be underambitious and succeed in a mundane way. I have been very fortunate. I failed upward in my life!', '"Life,My Life,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When I was sixteen or seventeen, I wanted to be a writer. I wanted to be a playwright. But everything I wrote, I thought, was weak. And I can remember falling asleep in tears because I had no talent the way I wanted to have."', '"Talent,Tears,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Anything you build on a large scale or with intense passion invites chaos.', '"Passion,Chaos,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'My film is not a movie; it\'s not about Vietnam. It is Vietnam.', '"Film,About,Vietnam"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Sound is your friend because sound is much cheaper than picture, but it has equal effect on the audience - in some ways, perhaps more effect because it does it in a very indirect way."', '"Way,Picture,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I don\'t go on set with an army of people because the most expensive elements of a movie production are the plane tickets, the hotel rooms, food and gasoline. If you\'re willing to discover new colleagues in the place that you are, you can save a ton of money."', '"Money,Food,Colleagues"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"You have to really be courageous about your instincts and your ideas. Otherwise you\'ll just knuckle under, and things that might have been memorable will be lost."', '"Courage,Lost,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Usually, the stuff that\'s your best idea or work is going to be attacked the most."', '"Work,Best,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Most Italians who came to this country are very patriotic. There was this exciting possibility that if you worked real hard, and you loved something, you could become successful."', '"Patriotism,Country,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When I was about 9, I had polio, and people were very frightened for their children, so you tended to be isolated. I was paralyzed for a while, so I watched television."', '"Children,People,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"\'The Godfather\' changed my life, for better or worse. It definitely made me have an older man\'s film career when I was 29."', '"Life,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Everything I do is personal. I have never made a movie that didn\'t have very strong personal resonance.', '"Never,Everything,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I believe that filmmaking - as, probably, is everything - is a game you should play with all your cards, and all your dice, and whatever else you\'ve got. So, each time I make a movie, I give it everything I have. I think everyone should, and I think everyone should do everything they do that way."', '"Time,Believe,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"It is a little disappointing to see that your legs are not as strong. But I like the idea of growing old, and the thought of approaching death is not particularly daunting to me."', '"Death,Me,See"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"If you\'re a person who says yes most of the time, you\'ll find yourself in the hotel business and the restaurant business."', '"Business,Time,Restaurant"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'We do things for good reasons that are bad.', '"Good,Bad,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I think a sequel is a waste of money and time. I think movies should illuminate new stories.', '"Money,Time,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I wrote the script of Patton. I had this very bizarre opening where he stands up in front of an American flag and gives this speech. Ultimately, I was fired. When the script was done, they hired another writer and that script was forgotten."', '"Done,Flag,American"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"In a sense, I think a movie is really a little like a question and when you make it, that\'s when you get the answer."', '"Answer,Think,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I probably have genius. But no talent.', '"Talent,Genius,No Talent"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"You ought to love what you\'re doing because, especially in a movie, over time you really will start to hate it."', '"Love,Time,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"The whole reason one wants to do lower budget films is because the lower the budget, the bigger the ideas, the bigger the themes, the more interesting the art."', '"Art,Ideas,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When I was going for my graduate degree, I decided I was going to make a feature film as my thesis. That\'s what I was famous for-that I had my thesis film be a feature film, which was \'You\'re a Big Boy Now.\'"', '"Graduation,Famous,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"It\'s ironic that at age 32, at probably the greatest moment of my career, with The Godfather having such an enormous success, I wasn\'t even aware of it, because I was somewhere else under the deadline again."', '"Success,Age,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I just admire people like Woody Allen, who every year writes an original screenplay. It\'s astonishing. I always wished that I could do that."', '"People,Always,Admire"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was never sloppy with other people\'s money. Only my own. Because I figure, well, you can be."', '"Money,People,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Some critics are stimulating in that they make you realise how you could do better, and those are valued."', '"Better,Critics,Realise"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Without a doubt, I was born to want to make cinema, but the kind of cinema I want to make is not like commercial movies, which I enjoy myself, but I wanted to be the kind of filmmaker who wrote original work, sort of like a novelist would who deals with who we are and our times or our relationships."', '"Work,Movies,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I know that if a film is ready to emerge out of what I write, I\'ll be able to go off and make it without asking anyone\'s permission."', '"Know,Go,Ready"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'It takes no imagination to live within your means.', '"Imagination,Live,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"In kindergarten that used to be my job, to tell them fairytales. I liked Hans Christian Andersen, and the Grimm fairy tales, all the classic fairy tales."', '"Fairy,Job,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I like to work in the morning. I like to sometimes go to a place where I\'m all alone where I\'m not going to get a phone call early that hurts my feelings, because once my feelings are hurt, I\'m dead in the water."', '"Alone,Work,Morning"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'George Lucas doesn\'t have the most physical stamina. He was so unhappy making Star Wars that he just vowed he\'d never do it again.', '"Unhappy,Never,He"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"The stuff that I got in trouble for, the casting for The Godfather or the flag scene in Patton, was the stuff that was remembered, and was considered the good work."', '"Work,Good,Good Work"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I have more of a vivid imagination than I have talent. I cook up ideas. It\'s just a characteristic.', '"Imagination,Talent,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I landed a job with Roger Corman. The job was to write the English dialogue for a Russian science fiction picture. I didn\'t speak any Russian. He didn\'t care whether I could understand what they were saying; he wanted me to make up dialogue.', '"Science,Me,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I gladly, I voluntarily gave up the kind of commercial film career I had going as soon as I had enough money to finance my own films."', '"Money,Finance,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Art depends on luck and talent.', '"Art,Talent,Luck"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was terrible at maths, but I could grasp science, and I used to love to read about the lives of the scientists. I wanted to be a scientist or an inventor."', '"Love,Science,Terrible"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I have much to learn from my daughter Sofia. Her minimalism exposes my limitations: I\'m too instinctive and operatic, I put too much heart into my work, I get lost sometimes in bizarre things - it\'s my Italian heritage."', '"Work,Heart,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"You\'re in a profession in which absolutely everybody is telling you their opinion, which is different. That\'s one of the reasons George Lucas never directed again."', '"Opinion,Never,Profession"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When I do a novel, I don\'t really use the script, I use the book; when I did Apocalypse Now, I used Heart of Darkness. Novels usually have so much rich material."', '"Heart,Darkness,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'They needed someone to write a script of The Great Gatsby very quickly for the movie they were making. I took this job so I\'d be sure to have some dough to support my family.', '"Family,Great,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'The professional world was much more unpleasant than I thought. I was always wishing I could get back that enthusiasm I had when I was doing shows at college.', '"World,Back,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Ten Days That Shook The World, by Eisenstein, I went to see it, and I was so impressed with this film, so impressed with what cinema could do."', '"Cinema,World,See"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Roger Corman exploited all of the young people who worked for him, but he really gave you responsibility and opportunity. So it was kind of a fair deal."', '"Opportunity,Responsibility,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was the kind of kid that had some talents or ability, but it never came out in school."', '"School,Never,Ability"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I thought I wanted to be a playwright because I was interested in stories and telling stories.', '"Because,Playwright,Interested"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I remember teachers who really singled me out for their discouragement.', '"Me,Remember,Teachers"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I remember growing up with television, from the time it was just a test pattern, with maybe a little bit of programming once in a while."', '"Time,Remember,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I liked to work in a shop down in the basement and invent things and build gadgets.', '"Work,Gadgets,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I had been a kid that moved so much, I didn\'t have a lot of friends. Theater really represented camaraderie."', '"Camaraderie,Friends,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I had an older brother who was very interested in literature, so I had an early exposure to literature, and and theater. My father sometimes would work in musical comedies."', '"Work,Father,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I had a number of very strong personalities in my family. My father was a concert flutist, the solo flute for Toscanini."', '"Family,Father,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I had a number of teachers who hated me. I didn\'t do well in school.', '"Me,School,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I had a heartbreaking experience when I was 9. I always wanted to be a guard. The most wonderful girl in the world was a guard. When I got polio and then went back to school, they made me a guard. A teacher took away my guard button."', '"Experience,Teacher,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I became quite successful very young, and it was mainly because I was so enthusiastic and I just worked so hard at it."', '"Young,Hard,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I associate my motion picture career more with being unhappy and scared, or being under the gun, than with anything pleasant."', '"Gun,Picture,Unhappy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I always found the film world unpleasant. It\'s all about the schedule, and never really flew for me."', '"Me,World,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Frank Capra was a prop man, I think. John Ford was a prop man. It was a little bit of a father and son thing, and you kind of worked your way up."', '"Man,Father,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'A number of images put together a certain way become something quite above and beyond what any of them are individually.', '"Together,Way,Beyond"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Listen, if there\'s one sure-fire rule that I have learned in this business, it\'s that I don\'t know anything about human nature."', '"Nature,Business,I Have Learned"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"All of a sudden, there are great Japanese films, or great Italian films, or great Australian films. It\'s usually because there are a number of people that cross-pollinated each other."', '"Great,People,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I bring to my life a certain amount of mess.', '"Life,My Life,Mess"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Steven Spielberg is unique. I feel that the kinds of movies he loves are the same kinds of movies that the big mass audience loves. He\'s very fortunate because he can do the things he naturally likes the best, and he\'s been very successful."', '"Best,Movies,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When newspapers started to publish the box office scores of movies, I was horrified. Those results are totally fake because they never include the promotion budget."', '"Movies,Fake,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I wanted to write and direct movies and not be forced to adapt them from a bestselling book.', '"Movies,Adapt,Book"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"As long as I can make lots of money in other businesses, I\'ll continue to subsidize my own work."', '"Work,Money,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I realized I probably wouldn\'t make another film that cuts through commercial and creative things like \'Godfather\' or \'Apocalypse.\'', '"Through,Film,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'The internet in hotels should be free - and I really resent it when they charge you five dollars for a bottle of water beside your bed.', '"Water,Free,Internet"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'The most adventurous thing I\'ve done is learn how to fly a helicopter in the Philippines. One night we landed on a beach and slept on it.', '"Night,Fly,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I used to love going into local hardware stores, to look at little things they made locally. Nowadays it\'s harder, though you can still do it in Vietnam."', '"Love,Look,Little Things"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I\'m no longer dependent on the movie business to make a living. So if I want to make movies as other old guys would play golf, I can."', '"Business,Movies,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Most filmmakers can\'t afford to try something out that doesn\'t work.', '"Work,Try,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I\'ve been offered lots of movies. There\'s always some actor who\'s doing a project and would like to have me do it. But you look at the project and think, \'Gee, there are a lot of good directors who could do that.\' I\'d like to do something only I can do."', '"Good,Movies,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"People feel the worst film I made was \'Jack.\' But to this day, when I get checks from old movies I\'ve made, \'Jack\' is one of the biggest ones. No one knows that. If people hate the movie, they hate the movie. I just wanted to work with Robin Williams."', '"Work,Movies,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Lots of people have criticized my movies, but nobody has ever identified the real problem: I\'m a sloppy filmmaker."', '"Movies,People,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I had to get a job, and of course, the job was \'The Godfather.\' That made me be something I didn\'t know I was going to be. I became a big-shot director."', '"Me,Know,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'When that happens - when risk is taken and the filmmakers dive into the subject matter without a parachute - very often what you get it something with those qualities that make it age well with the public.', '"Age,Matter,Dive"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'My big goal in life was always to figure out how I can make a lot of money so I can go off and make films irrespective of the opinion of the three or four critics who seem to rule the roost.', '"Life,Money,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Anyone who\'s made film and knows about the cinema has a lifelong love affair with the experience. You never stop learning about film.', '"Love,Experience,Learning"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"That\'s part of the requirement for me to be an artist is that you\'re trying to share your personal existence with others and trying to illuminate modern life, trying to understand life."', '"Life,Me,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"By working in the morning, I find a sense of peace; it\'s isolated peace, but I can definitely be in touch with my feelings, and then I just start."', '"Peace,Morning,Feelings"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"\'Godfather\' was very classical - the way it was shot, the style - the whole driving force of it was more classical, almost Shakespearean."', '"Style,Way,More"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When a movie is about to come out on its initial debut, there are a lot of people involved - the financiers, the studio and the producers and also, many times, the foreign distributors. So it is a time of tremendous pressure and uncertainty."', '"Time,Uncertainty,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Being a former theater student, of course, there is a part of me that is fascinated with stage crafts and what you can do with illusions and working within the confines of the studio."', '"Me,Stage,Student"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"When I was 13, I worked for Western Union. When the telegrams came in, I would glue them on the paper and deliver them on my bicycle."', '"Bicycle,Deliver,Paper"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'We support each other in the Coppola family. We love the idea of everyone getting his place in the sun.', '"Love,Family,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Movie-wise, there is nothing I wouldn\'t do again. It\'s not possible to make one perfect movie every time."', '"Time,Perfect,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I never went to a psychologist or psychiatrist in my life. Never. You know, Italians are a little prejudiced against that kind of thing."', '"Life,My Life,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"If I have to be remembered for something, I want it remembered that I really liked children and was a good camp counselor."', '"Good,Children,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'I\'ve been offered lots of movies. There\'s always some actor who\'s doing a project and would like to have me do it.', '"Movies,Me,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'Sequels are not done for the audience or cinema or the filmmakers. It\'s for the distributor. The film becomes a brand.', '"Cinema,Done,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', 'The only TV I would be interested in exploring would be live television. There\'s no substitute for a team of artists performing at their peak live when failure is possible. It\'s a high-wire act. That excites me.', '"Failure,Me,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"Films and hotels have many aspects that are the same. For example, there is always a big vision, an idea."', '"Vision,Big,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I\'ve been blessed with enough wealth that I can make a film myself up to a certain budget. So one way I thought I would reinvent myself was just to make these very small, personal films that I\'ve financed myself."', '"Myself,Blessed,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"My company and people think I\'m wacky when I have an idea... I know if I have an idea, no one will want to go through it. But if I persist, people will go through it."', '"People,Will,Company"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I wanted to be a film student again, as a man in my 60s. To go someplace alone and see what you can cook up, with non-existent budgets. I didn\'t want to be surrounded by comforts and colleagues, which you have when when you\'re a big time director. I wanted to write personal works."', '"Alone,Time,Colleagues"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I was a pretty shy, lonely kid. I blossomed about age 17, when I went to college."', '"Age,Shy,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"My family were symphonic musicians and in the opera. Also, it was my era, the love of radio. We used to listen to the radio at night, close our eyes and see movies far more beautiful than you can photograph."', '"Love,Family,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"To make great movies, there is an element of risk. You have to say, \'Well, I am going to make this film, and it is not really a sure thing.\'"', '"Great,Movies,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"The time a movie is made is unique, not only from the talent that is available but if the public was ready for it."', '"Time,Talent,Unique"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc4', '"I live near San Francisco in the most beautiful spot on earth and enjoy myself in many ways. Yes, I love to work, which for now is to think and read and write, so it\'s all a dream come true."', '"Love,Work,Most Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', '"In general, Americans are not very good at nation-building and not very good colonialists."', '"Good,General,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', 'I\'m a tenured professor. But I\'d get rid of tenure.', '"Get,Tenure,Professor"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', '"I\'ve always had a Marxist understanding of history: democracy is a result of a broad modernization process that happens in every country. Neocons think the use of political power can force the pace of change, but ultimately it depends on societies doing it themselves."', '"Change,History,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', '"I\'m basically an optimist because I do think there\'s this historical modernisation process, and by and large it\'s been very beneficial to people. But there are blips. History doesn\'t proceed in a linear way."', '"History,Process,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', '"I\'ve figured out in the course of my life that the one thing I\'m good at doing is writing books, and it would be crazy to trade that in for something else."', '"Life,Good,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc5', '"The rationale for tenure is still valid. But the system has turned the academy into one of the most conservative and costly institutions in the country. Yes, conservative: Economists joke that their discipline advances one funeral at a time, but many fields must wait for wholesale generational turnover before new approaches take hold."', '"Time,Discipline,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc6', '"I plan to see St. Louis as a global competitor. As an international trade hub, as an incubator of new companies, as a place of culture and the arts, as a magnet for immigrants, for entrepreneurs, for animal lovers, and for gays, as a city of parks and trails, and as the sort of place that figures in young people\'s dreams."', '"Dreams,Culture,City"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc6', 'Violence is not a constitutionally protected right. Damaging property is not a constitutionally protected right; inciting violence is not a constitutionally protected right.', '"Violence,Right,Property"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc8', '"What we need most, is not so much to realize the ideal as to idealize the real."', '"Real,Realize,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc8', '"Talent is a faculty that is highly developed, but genius commands all the faculties."', '"Brainy,Talent,Genius"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc8', 'Sympathy with nature is part of a good person\'s religion.', '"Nature,Good,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc8', '"Every man is his own ancestor, and every man his own heir. He devises his own fortune, and he inherits his own past."', '"Man,Past,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc9', 'Wisdom denotes the pursuing of the best ends by the best means.', '"Wisdom,Best,Means"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdc9', 'That action is best which procures the greatest happiness for the greatest numbers.', '"Happiness,Best,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdca', 'All is lost save honor.', '"Lost,Honor,Save"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdca', 'Woman is always fickle - foolish is he who trusts her.', '"Woman,Always,Fickle"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdca', '"There is nothing left to me but honor, and my life, which is saved."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdca', '"Persons famous in the arts partake of the immortality of princes, and are upon a footing with them."', '"Famous,Immortality,Them"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcb', '"Race prejudice can\'t be talked down, it must be lived down."', '"Race,Down,Prejudice"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcb', 'It is only what is written upon the soul of man that will survive the wreck of time.', '"Time,Man,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcb', 'A pretty good test of a man\'s religion is how it affects his pocketbook.', '"Good,Religion,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcc', '"Good will, like a good name, is got by many actions, and lost by one."', '"Good,Lost,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcc', 'The tendency to whining and complaining may be taken as the surest sign symptom of little souls and inferior intellects.', '"Complaining,May,Inferior"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcc', 'There is nothing respecting which a man may be so long unconscious as of the extent and strength of his prejudices.', '"Strength,Man,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcc', '"Beware prejudices. They are like rats, and men\'s minds are like traps; prejudices get in easily, but it is doubtful if they ever get out."', '"Men,Beware,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcd', 'We must get away from the idea that America is to be the leader of the world in everything.', '"World,America,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcd', 'We need a type of patriotism that recognizes the virtues of those who are opposed to us.', '"Patriotism,Virtues,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I wish that the circuses that were around now felt like they did then. They\'re not quite as elegant or as magical as they used to be. There was something about the old tent shows, the Big Top, the canvas, the lights, the sawdust, the hay and the animals that\'s just missing now. Now, it\'s all urbanized and maybe a little garish."', '"Canvas,Wish,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I believe that the process could be fun, I just think that making movies is really tough. And it\'s stressful as it is, and I think that most of us got in this business because it\'s fun to make movies."', '"Business,Movies,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I think the movie business and film crews are a little bit like the circus, in that we travel around like a pack and we\'re a big family for a finite period of time. We roll into someplace, cause a bunch of damage, and then roll out."', '"Family,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"Whenever you\'re adapting something that\'s a 12- or 14-hour read down to something that has to be around two hours, there\'s going to be some cuts."', '"Down,Two,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I think that the thing that is really strong with \'The Hunger Games\' is just that it comes from a very strong idea.', '"Strong,Hunger,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"There are two separate scripts for \'Mockingjay\' parts one and two. It\'s definitely one story, but there are two totally distinct and separate scripts."', '"Story,Two,Separate"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I\'ve been a fan of noir films since I was in high school.', '"School,Fan,High School"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"One of the big themes - if not the big theme - of \'Mockingjay - Part 1\' is the battle of the airwaves. I don\'t think teenagers really understand the role propaganda has in our lives in terms of politics, advertising, and the general manipulation of imagery."', '"Politics,Battle,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"\'I Am Legend\' was a rich, emotional experience where you could be scared and cry, and there\'s some wish fulfilment."', '"Experience,Legend,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I love animals. Even if you go back to my music video days, I can\'t tell you how many animals I used."', '"Love,Music,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"When you\'re making a movie, you have those days that you really look forward to, and it\'s a little bit like Murphy\'s law. The days you look forward to become your hell days. The days you\'re dreading become these amazing days."', '"Amazing,Look,Hell"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I\'ve never seen a \'Transporter\' movie.', '"Never,Seen,Movie"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"Often, adults don\'t give kids enough credit."', '"Credit,Enough,Kids"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"All the \'Hunger Games\' stuff, we had a fantastic production designer, and he built amazing sets."', '"Amazing,Hunger,He"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I love reluctant heroes, all of that."', '"Love,Heroes,Reluctant"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I never... it\'s a hard thing: when I think about projects, I don\'t come off something and go, \'I really want to make a sci-fi film next,\' or \'I really want to do a political thriller next.\' It\'s really coming across - I\'m really fascinated, partly by world building, but also about the character and what the journey is."', '"Journey,Character,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"It\'s kind of the filmmaker\'s job to use visual, cinematic language in a way possible to tell a story that reaches and touches as many people as possible."', '"Way,People,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"I always want to try to make films feel timeless, because one of my biggest pet peeves is that there\'s a movie you love, and then you revisit it twenty years later, you show your kid or something, and it\'s like, \'Oh my God!\' with hairstyles and clothing and all that kind of stuff."', '"Love,God,Pet"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'We actually started shooting the \'Mockingjay\' movies before \'Catching Fire\' was released.', '"Movies,Fire,Shooting"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I\'m attracted to the journeys of isolated characters.', '"Attracted,Journeys,Isolated"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I still wear Vans.', '"Wear,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I remember \'Battlestar Galactica\' shot at the college that my dad taught at. I remember trying on a Cylon helmet. I think I was 6 or 7 years old.', '"Dad,Remember,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '"When I signed on and went and did \'Catching Fire,\' the majority of it was done in Atlanta for rebate reasons. Luckily, that worked because there\'s forest. There\'s old rail stations and factories and lots of stuff we can use and sound stages. For the tropical stuff, we went to Hawaii."', '"Fire,Done,Sound"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', 'I\'ve now made enough movies that I understand that people love to put things in a box.', '"Love,Movies,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '\'Last Man on Earth\'... Vincent Price is one of my favorite actors; I think he was miscast.', '"Man,Earth,Price"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdce', '\'Omega Man\' is a little too tied to a specific generation and a little cult-y to me.', '"Man,Me,Generation"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcf', '"I\'m dumbfounded, but nothing surprises me in this game."', '"Me,Game,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcf', '"Manchester was a fantastic place to go out in. There were 10 clubs with world-class cabaret and comedians. You\'d go in and Tom Jones might be singing, or Shirley Bassey or Engelbert Humperdinck."', '"Singing,Place,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcf', 'You don\'t have to be popular with the players to be a good manager or coach.', '"Good,Players,Coach"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdcf', 'I would love to have played with David Silva.', '"Love,Would,David"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd0', '"No one will ever shine in conversation, who thinks of saying fine things: to please, one must say many things indifferent, and many very bad."', '"Bad,Shine,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd0', '"The one book necessary to be understood by a divine, is the Bible; any others are to be read, chiefly, in order to understand that."', '"Bible,Divine,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('395999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd0', '"In all my travels I never met with any one Scotchman but what was a man of sense: I believe everybody of that country that has any, leaves it as fast as they can."', '"Man,Believe,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd1', 'To expect defeat is nine-tenths of defeat itself.', '"Defeat,Expect,Itself"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd1', 'No one person can possibly combine all the elements supposed to make up what everyone means by friendship.', '"Friendship,Person,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'It always seemed to me a bit pointless to disapprove of homosexuality. It\'s like disapproving of rain.', '"Rain,Me,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'I feel fantastically excited that we have a leader who fought for the leadership without compromising his quite challenging view that the party has to change.', '"Leadership,Change,View"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"Our members are very much maligned. Obviously the average age is 60 something, but they all have children and grandchildren, they understand what we need to do, they want to win."', '"Age,Children,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"If we do what we think is right, not try to point-score, people will begin to trust us."', '"Trust,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'But if we can work with people in other parties to get the right answer for the country we\'ll do that.', '"Work,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"They don\'t think we\'re in touch with modern Britain, or understand modern Britain or like modern Britain."', '"Understand,Touch,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'The party at its best has always been a modern party.', '"Best,Always,Modern"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"We said in our 21st Century Party paper there are 61 mosaic groups, which the market research people use as different socio-economic categories and half of our members come from just five of those groups and that is very narrow - too narrow."', '"Research,People,Paper"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"For the most part our grassroots members are serious, nice, tolerant people."', '"People,Serious,Nice"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"It is simply the view, and a view I think shared by most members of the party, that it is very difficult to have a leader that does not command the support of the parliamentary party."', '"View,Support,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"The problem we have is not Labour, in however it is configured."', '"Problem,Labour,However"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"So our problem is not Labour, it is us, is making us attractive enough to gain disillusioned Labour support and to compete effectively with the Lib Dems for those loose votes."', '"Support,Enough,Attractive"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'We need to show that we know and understand and can reflect today\'s Britain. Today we don\'t.', '"Today,Know,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"Our share of the vote overall rose by less than 1 per cent - yes, that\'s right: less than 1 per cent."', '"Right,Vote,Rose"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'We should be the natural home for the millions of Britons of immigrant origin. But we\'re not. Because too often we\'ve sounded like people who wish they hadn\'t come here at all.', '"Home,People,Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"Our party believes in diversity, not uniformity."', '"Diversity,Party,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'Our party\'s committed to tackling failing schools and cutting crime.', '"Party,Our,Failing"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'We should be the natural home for younger voters. But today we\'re not. Because too often we sound like people who just don\'t like contemporary Britain.', '"Home,Today,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', 'We should be the natural home for young mothers. But we\'re not. Because too often we sound like people who think the only good mother is a married mother.', '"Good,Home,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"If we want to change what people think of us, then we have got to change."', '"Change,People,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd2', '"Our party has known great, great days. But we have no God-given right to survive, let alone to succeed."', '"Alone,Great,Survive"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"The one who intimidates me is myself. I\'m scared to fail. That is the thing that makes me the most afraid, to fail. Just to think that I can do a mistake and lose the fight scares me, so that is why I work out a lot: to bring more chance to my size and less chance to my opponent."', '"Work,Chance,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', 'I\'m going to make my own heaven. I\'m going to struggle for it. I\'m going to fight to earn everything I dream about.', '"Struggle,Fight,Heaven"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"Just do what you do. Sometimes you do well, and sometimes you do wrong, but you have to just be able to deal with yourself and move forward."', '"Yourself,Sometimes,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"When you\'re used to having nothing, the first time you have something, you get really focused. You know if you lose it, it may not be easy to get it back."', '"Time,Lose,First Time"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"Listen to what I\'m saying: I\'m back. Junior Dos Santos, Alexander Volkov, or revenge against Stipe Miocic. That fight, I didn\'t do well, and I really want to fix it."', '"Revenge,Fight,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"Speed is something that, in the heavyweight division, we don\'t have a lot of."', '"Speed,Something,Division"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"In Cameroon, kids have many problems. They think everything is lost before they are born. It seems like they are not allowed to dream. They are not allowed to be ambitious. They just accept being the victim of their life."', '"Life,Problems,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"Watching some heavyweights like Mike Tyson, he inspired me to work with my speed because he beat people with power, but most of the time, he beat people with speed."', '"Work,Time,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', 'People easily quit their dream because it\'s not easy.', '"People,Easy,Quit"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', 'I keep my head straight toward my goal.', '"Head,Straight,Keep"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', 'The most important thing for me is to win the fight and not what people are going to say.', '"Fight,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', 'The biggest win of my career is coming.', '"Win,Coming,Career"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"I am building a foundation in Cameroon, and it\'s not just about the sport. The goal of the foundation is not to make a UFC fighter. It\'s to help kids believe in their dream, to have a dream, to have a purpose in life."', '"Life,Believe,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"I\'ve been in this sport only four years, and I know that I\'ll keep learning and improving."', '"Learning,Know,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"As a challenger, I need and want to fight some people because that would give me the opportunity to get to the title shot."', '"Opportunity,Fight,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"At the beginning, my dream was to become a world-class boxer, but then I stepped into MMA. And when I stepped into MMA, it was to have fun. I reminded myself of what was the purpose, of what was the goal: to have fun."', '"Myself,Purpose,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"There are a lot of people out there who want to fight me. I saw Mark Hunt; he would be a great one. By myself, I want Brock. Brock Lesnar."', '"Great,Myself,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd3', '"People told me, \'You talk about Europe like it\'s Heaven. It\'s not Heaven."', '"Me,People,Heaven"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Start by doing what\'s necessary; then do what\'s possible; and suddenly you are doing the impossible.', '"Inspirational,Impossible,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Lord, make me an instrument of thy peace. Where there is hatred, let me sow love."', '"Love,Peace,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'A single sunbeam is enough to drive away many shadows.', '"Inspirational,Drive,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:52:00', '2023-05-29 11:52:00'),
	('396044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"While you are proclaiming peace with your lips, be careful to have it even more fully in your heart."', '"Peace,Heart,Lips"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'For it is in giving that we receive.', '"Christmas,Giving,Receive"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"If God can work through me, he can work through anyone."', '"Work,God,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'It is no use walking anywhere to preach unless our walking is our preaching.', '"Walking,Use,Preaching"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Men lose all the material things they leave behind them in this world, but they carry with them the reward of their charity and the alms they give. For these, they will receive from the Lord the reward and recompense they deserve."', '"Men,World,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'It is in pardoning that we are pardoned.', '"Forgiveness,Pardoned"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Where there is charity and wisdom, there is neither fear nor ignorance."', '"Wisdom,Fear,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Lord, grant that I might not so much seek to be loved as to love."', '"Love,Loved,Lord"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"If a superior give any order to one who is under him which is against that man\'s conscience, although he do not obey it yet he shall not be dismissed."', '"Man,Conscience,Obey"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"If you have men who will exclude any of God\'s creatures from the shelter of compassion and pity, you will have men who will deal likewise with their fellow men."', '"God,Men,Compassion"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Above all the grace and the gifts that Christ gives to his beloved is that of overcoming self.', '"Grace,Self,Overcoming"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"No one is to be called an enemy, all are your benefactors, and no one does you harm. You have no enemy except yourselves."', '"Enemy,Your,Harm"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"It is not fitting, when one is in God\'s service, to have a gloomy face or a chilling look."', '"God,Look,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Praised be You, my Lord, through our Sister, Mother Earth, who sustains and governs us, producing varied fruits with coloured flowers and herbs."', '"Earth,Flowers,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Where there is injury let me sow pardon.', '"Me,Injury,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Great and glorious God, and Thou Lord Jesus, I pray you shed abroad your light in the darkness of my mind. Be found of me, Lord, so that in all things I may act only in accordance with Thy holy will."', '"God,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"We must not be wise and prudent according to the flesh. Rather, we must be simple, humble and pure."', '"Wise,Humble,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Holy humility confounds pride and all the men of this world and all things that are in the world.', '"Men,Pride,World"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Praised be You, my Lord, through Sister Moon and the stars; in the heavens, you have made them bright, precious and fair."', '"Moon,Stars,Precious"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Grant me the treasure of sublime poverty: permit the distinctive sign of our order to be that it does not possess anything of its own beneath the sun, for the glory of your name, and that it have no other patrimony than begging."', '"Me,Sun,Poverty"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"We should never desire to be over others. Instead, we ought to be servants who are submissive to every human being for God\'s sake."', '"God,Never,Desire"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"The Father willed that his blessed and glorious Son, whom he gave to us and who was born for us, should through his own blood offer himself as a sacrificial victim on the altar of the cross. This was to be done not for himself through whom all things were made, but for our sins."', '"Father,Blessed,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Pure, holy simplicity confounds all the wisdom of this world and the wisdom of the flesh."', '"Wisdom,World,Simplicity"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Holy poverty confounds cupidity and avarice and the cares of this world.', '"World,Poverty,Holy"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Praised be You, my Lord, with all Your creatures, especially Sir Brother Sun, Who is the day through whom You give us light. And he is beautiful and radiant with great splendour; of You, Most High, he bears the likeness."', '"Great,Beautiful,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Holy wisdom confounds Satan and all his wickednesses.', '"Wisdom,Satan,Holy"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'I am the herald of the Great King.', '"Great,King,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', '"Praised be You, my Lord, through Brother Fire, through whom You light the night, and he is beautiful and playful and robust and strong."', '"Beautiful,Fire,Night"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Woe to those who die in mortal sin!', '"Die,Sin,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddf', 'Holy charity confounds all diabolical and fleshly temptations and all fleshly fears.', '"Charity,Holy,Fears"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Alliance does not mean love, any more than war means hate."', '"Love,War,Hate"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Capitalism is not an economic system, but a world-outlook, or rather, a part of a whole world-outlook."', '"Capitalism,System,Rather"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"A moment\'s reflection shows that Liberalism is entirely negative. It is not a formative force, but always and only a disintegrating force."', '"Moment,Reflection,Negative"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Hatred is not contained in political thinking. Any hatred worked up against the public enemy is non-political, and always shows some weakness in the internal political situation."', '"Political,Thinking,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Rationalism, which is the feeling that everything is subject to and completely explicable by Reason, consequently rejects everything not visible and calculable."', '"Everything,Reason,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"The important part of Marxism was its demand for active, constant, practical, class-war."', '"Important,Active,Demand"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Liberalism is a most important by-product of Rationalism, and its origins and ideology must be clearly shown."', '"Important,Ideology,Liberalism"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"If pessimism is despair, optimism is cowardice and stupidity. Is there any need to choose between them?"', '"Stupidity,Optimism,Choose"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'The independence of the economic sphere was a tenet of faith with Liberalism.', '"Faith,Independence,Liberalism"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"The State becomes society or humanity on the ethical side, a production and trade system on the economic side."', '"Society,Humanity,Side"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'No section of the American populace has been more completely deceived by the forces interested in keeping the truth from the people than America\'s youth.', '"Truth,Youth,America"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"As a world view, Darwinism cannot of course be refuted, since Faith is, always has been, and always will be, stronger than facts."', '"Faith,View,World"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Pessimism only describes an attitude, and not facts, and hence is entirely subjective."', '"Attitude,Facts,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'Politics is activity in relation to power.', '"Politics,Power,Activity"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'The 19th century was the age of Individualism; the 20th and 21st are the ages of Socialism.', '"Age,Socialism,Individualism"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'The purest expression of the doctrine of Liberalism was probably that of Benjamin Constant.', '"Expression,Liberalism,Constant"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'The early American arrived at a land of which he knew nothing.', '"Nothing,American,Land"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'Liberalism is Rationalism in politics.', '"Politics,Liberalism,Rationalism"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Liberalism can only be defined negatively. It is a mere critique, not a living idea."', '"Living,Only,Liberalism"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"To an intellectual who is adrift in politics, a theory is an aim; to a true politician his theory is a boundary."', '"Politics,Aim,True"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'A political theory seeks to find from history the limits of the politically possible.', '"History,Political,Limits"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"To the fantastic mental illness of Rationalism, hard facts are regrettable things, and to talk about them is to create them."', '"Facts,Create,Talk"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'The way politics divides the world is into friend and enemy.', '"Politics,World,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', '"Every non-political human grouping of whatever kind, legal, social, religious, economic or other becomes at last political if it creates an opposition deep enough to range men against one another as enemies."', '"Men,Legal,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'Leftist ideas are a part of the very atmosphere which American youth breathes.', '"Youth,Ideas,American"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'Man as a pure animal does not exist.', '"Man,Animal,Pure"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd4', 'Every science is a profane restatement of the preceding dogmas of the religious period.', '"Science,Every,Religious"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'It was a rich and gorgeous sunset - an American sunset; and the ruddy glow of the sky was reflected from some extensive pools of water among the shadowy copses in the meadow below.', '"Sky,Water,Glow"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'The fortified towns of the Hurons were all on the side exposed to Iroquois incursions.', '"Side,Fortified,Exposed"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"We were soon free of the woods and bushes, and fairly upon the broad prairie."', '"Free,Woods,Soon"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Not a breath of air stirred over the free and open prairie; the clouds were like light piles of cotton; and where the blue sky was visible, it wore a hazy and languid aspect."', '"Sky,Clouds,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"We were now, as I before mentioned, upon this St. Joseph\'s trail. It was evident, by the traces, that large parties were a few days in advance of us; and as we too supposed them to be Mormons, we had some apprehension of interruption."', '"Us,Trail,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Crossing the Penobscot, one found a visible descent in the scale of humanity."', '"Humanity,Found,Crossing"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'A few hours\' ride brought us to the banks of the river Kansas.', '"River,Ride,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"A military road led from this point to Fort Leavenworth, and for many miles the farms and cabins of the Delawares were scattered at short intervals on either hand."', '"Road,Miles,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"America, when it became known to Europeans, was, as it had long been, a scene of wide-spread revolution."', '"Long,America,Revolution"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Early on the next morning we reached Kansas, about five hundred miles from the mouth of the Missouri."', '"Morning,Mouth,Miles"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Fort Leavenworth is in fact no fort, being without defensive works, except two block-houses."', '"Two,Fort,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Four men are missing; R., Sorel and two emigrants. They set out this morning after buffalo, and have not yet made their appearance; whether killed or lost, we cannot tell."', '"Morning,Men,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Here society is reduced to its original elements, the whole fabric of art and conventionality is struck rudely to pieces, and men find themselves suddenly brought back to the wants and resources of their original natures."', '"Men,Art,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Many of the Iroquois and Huron houses were of similar construction, the partitions being at the sides only, leaving a wide passage down the middle of the house."', '"Construction,Down,House"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'Our New England climate is mild and equable compared with that of the Platte.', '"New,Climate,England"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"Riding in advance, we passed over one of these great plains; we looked back and saw the line of scattered horsemen stretching for a mile or more; and far in the rear against the horizon, the white wagons creeping slowly along."', '"Great,Horizon,White"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"The great medley of Oregon and California emigrants, at their camps around Independence, had heard reports that several additional parties were on the point of setting out from St. Joseph\'s farther to the northward."', '"Great,Independence,Point"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'The reader need not be told that John Bull never leaves home without encumbering himself with the greatest possible load of luggage. Our companions were no exception to the rule.', '"Home,Never,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', '"We were in all four men with eight animals; for besides the spare horses led by Shaw and myself, an additional mule was driven along with us as a reserve in case of accident."', '"Men,Myself,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd5', 'We were now arrived at the close of our solitary journeyings along the St. Joseph\'s trail.', '"Trail,Now,Close"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', '"If you want to have clean ideas, change them as often as your shirt."', '"Change,Shirt,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Good taste is as tiring as good company.', '"Good,Good Company,Company"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Let us never forget that the greatest man is never more than an animal disguised as a god.', '"God,Man,Never Forget"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Only useless things are indispensable.', '"Useless,Things,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'My ass contemplates those who talk behind my back.', '"Back,Talk,Behind"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'The world is divided into two categories: failures and unknowns.', '"Failure,World,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'My arse contemplates those who talk behind my back.', '"Back,Talk,Behind"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Knowledge is ancient error reflecting on its youth.', '"Knowledge,Youth,Error"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', '"Pain has its reasons, pleasure is totally indifferent."', '"Pain,Pleasure,Indifferent"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'A free spirit takes liberties even with liberty itself.', '"Free,Liberty,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', '"God invented concubinage, satan marriage."', '"God,Marriage,Satan"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'The essence of a man is found in his faults.', '"Man,Essence,Faults"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'A new gadget that lasts only five minutes is worth more than an immortal work that bores everyone.', '"Work,New,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', '"Between my head and my hand, there is always the face of death."', '"Death,Face,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'The family spirit has rendered man carnivorous.', '"Family,Man,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Men have always need of god! A god to defend them against other men.', '"God,Men,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', 'Maybe men are separated from each other only by the degree of their misery.', '"Men,Degree,Misery"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd6', '"Youth doesn\'t reason, it acts. The old man reasons and would like to make the others act in his place."', '"Youth,Man,Old Man"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Beware of him that is slow to anger; for when it is long coming, it is the stronger when it comes, and the longer kept. Abused patience turns to fury."', '"Patience,Anger,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'My mind\'s my kingdom.', '"Inspirational,Mind,Kingdom"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'That friendship will not continue to the end which is begun for an end.', '"Friendship,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'He that hath no cross deserves no crown.', '"Crown,He,Cross"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'The sufficiency of merit is to know that my merit is not sufficient.', '"Know,Merit,Sufficient"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'Has fortune dealt you some bad cards. Then let wisdom make you a good gamester.', '"Wisdom,Good,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'No cross no crown.', '"Crown,Cross"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Be wisely worldly, but not worldly wise."', '"Wise,Wisely,Worldly"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Luxury is an enticing pleasure, a bastard mirth, which hath honey in her mouth, gall in her heart, and a sting in her tail."', '"Heart,Honey,Mouth"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Let the fear of danger be a spur to prevent it; he that fears not, gives advantage to the danger."', '"Fear,Danger,He"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"If thou desire the love of God and man, be humble, for the proud heart, as it loves none but itself, is beloved of none but itself. Humility enforces where neither virtue, nor strength, nor reason can prevail."', '"Love,God,Strength"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"The heart is a small thing, but desireth great matters. It is not sufficient for a kite\'s dinner, yet the whole world is not sufficient for it."', '"Great,Heart,World"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'Wickedness is its own punishment.', '"Punishment,Own,Wickedness"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Temper your enjoyments with prudence, lest there be written on your heart that fearful word \'satiety.\'"', '"Heart,Temper,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Meditation is the life of the soul: Action, the soul of meditation; and honor the reward of action."', '"Life,Soul,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Necessity of action takes away the fear of the act, and makes bold resolution the favorite of fortune."', '"Fear,Action,Bold"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'And he repents in thorns that sleeps in beds of roses.', '"Roses,Thorns,He"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Anger may repast with thee for an hour, but not repose for a night; the continuance of anger is hatred, the continuance of hatred turns malice."', '"Anger,Night,Hatred"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'Heaven finds an ear when sinners find a tongue.', '"Heaven,Find,Tongue"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"The average person\'s ear weighs what you are, not what you were."', '"Person,Ear,Average"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Put off thy cares with thy clothes; so shall thy rest strengthen thy labor, and so thy labor sweeten thy rest."', '"Work,Rest,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'It is the lot of man but once to die.', '"Man,Die,Once"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'The road to perseverance lies by doubt.', '"Perseverance,Road,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'Flatter not thyself in thy faith in God if thou hast not charity for thy neighbor.', '"Faith,God,Neighbor"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', 'Fear nothing but what thy industry may prevent; be confident of nothing but what fortune cannot defeat; it is no less folly to fear what is impossible to be avoided than to be secure when there is a possibility to be deprived.', '"Fear,Impossible,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"Wisdom not only gets, but once got, retains."', '"Wisdom,Only,Once"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd7', '"I wish thee as much pleasure in the reading, as I had in the writing."', '"Wish,Pleasure,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', 'Biblical orthodoxy without compassion is surely the ugliest thing in the world.', '"World,Compassion,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', '"I believe that pluralistic secularism, in the long run, is a more deadly poison than straightforward persecution."', '"Believe,Long,I Believe That"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', '"Each generation of the church in each setting has the responsibility of communicating the gospel in understandable terms, considering the language and thought-forms of that setting."', '"Responsibility,Generation,Church"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', 'Christianity is the greatest intellectual system the mind of man has ever touched.', '"Man,Mind,Intellectual"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', 'I have come to the conclusion that none of us in our generation feels as guilty about sin as we should or as our forefathers did.', '"Generation,Sin,Guilty"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', '"In passing, we should note this curious mark of our own age: the only absolute allowed is the absolute insistence that there is no absolute."', '"Age,Curious,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', 'Christianity provides a unified answer for the whole of life.', '"Life,Answer,Christianity"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', '"The inward area is the first place of loss of true Christian life, of true spirituality, and the outward sinful act is the result."', '"Life,Result,True"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd8', '"Doctrinal rightness and rightness of ecclesiastical position are important, but only as a starting point to go on into a living relationship - and not as ends in themselves."', '"Relationship,Important,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd9', 'Their blood has washed out their foul footsteps\' pollution. No refuge could save the hireling and slave from the terror of flight or the gloom of the grave.', '"Blood,Pollution,Flight"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd9', '"The patriot who feels himself in the service of God, who acknowledges Him in all his ways, has the promise of Almighty direction, and will find His Word in his greatest darkness."', '"God,Service,Darkness"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd9', '"Then, in that hour of deliverance, my heart spoke. Does not such a country, and such defenders of their country, deserve a song?"', '"Heart,Song,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdd9', '"He will therefore seek to establish for his country in the eyes of the world, such a character as shall make her not unworthy of the name of a Christian nation."', '"Eyes,Character,World"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"What I absolutely want is to suggest that before it\'s anything else, redemption is God mending the bicycle of our souls; God bringing out the puncture repair kit, re-inflating the tires, taking off the rust, making us roadworthy once more. Not so that we can take flight into ecstasy, but so that we can do the next needful mile of our lives."', '"God,Bicycle,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"In a hundred years, Christianity will have mutated into something utterly unpredictable which, nevertheless, we\'d recognize immediately. And same-sex marriage will be one of the fine old God-given traditions that conservatives leap to defend."', '"Marriage,Will,Unpredictable"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Emotions can certainly be misleading: they can fool you into believing stuff that is definitely, demonstrably untrue."', '"Fool,Emotions,Believing"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Belief demands that you dispense with illusion after illusion, while contemporary common sense requires continual, fluffy pretending - pretending that might as well be systematic, it\'s so thoroughly incentivised by our culture."', '"Culture,Illusion,Common Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"I was never argued out of faith; it was much more passive than that - and I wasn\'t argued back in, either."', '"Faith,Back,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"It\'s true that when Christianity is socially powerful, faith can look from the outside as if it is mainly a matter of membership, of participation in the vast synchronised swim of institutions."', '"Faith,Look,True"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"For a believer, Christian faith is true to the human heart, not in the sense that any old thing we fancy believing in will become conveniently true - but because the complicated truth about our hearts, as we struggle to perceive it, tells us what we are and where we are, and consequently what we need."', '"Faith,Truth,Heart"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"The emotions that sustain religious belief are all, in fact, deeply ordinary and deeply recognisable to anybody who has ever made their way across the common ground of human experience as an adult."', '"Experience,Emotions,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"If you based your knowledge of the human species exclusively on adverts, you\'d think that the normal condition of humanity was to be a good-looking single person between 20 and 35, with excellent muscle-definition and/or an excellent figure, and a large disposable income."', '"Knowledge,Humanity,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"There have been low moments before, but Christianity is an incredibly adaptable organism, using different parts of its repertoire to mutate into new ecological niches, yet preserving intact its story of grace, of love improbably triumphant."', '"Love,Grace,New"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"I think I have made allowances for the kind of despair which would test my faith, but you cannot know in advance what disaster to those you love would be too much to bear faithfully, and like everyone\'s, my faith is weakly conditional in some ways. I hope, I pray not to lose it. My fingers are crossed. Also my heart."', '"Love,Faith,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', 'What we need in Europe is to push back against the idea that religion is so farfetched that it\'s not worth talking about.', '"Religion,Back,Worth"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Christianity is a religion of continuity and discontinuity as well. It\'s about what stays the same and what changes in the twinkling of an eye. Both are necessary truths, but sometimes it\'s important to accentuate the discontinuity, the sudden leap, the way you go up a tree, Zacchaeus, and come down a saint."', '"Religion,Tree,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Christians are as subject to complacency as anybody else, and we can certainly settle into repetition and forget that something radical and extraordinary is being asked of us as well - that we hold to an extraordinary promise about how, from moment to moment, something enters the world and enters us, after which everything is different."', '"Moment,World,Complacency"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"I am a fairly orthodox Christian. Every Sunday, I say and do my best to mean the whole of the Creed, which is a series of propositions. But it is still a mistake to suppose that it is assent to the propositions that makes you a believer. It is the feelings that are primary."', '"Best,I Am,Mistake"', '2023-05-29 11:53:00', '2023-05-29 11:53:00'),
	('396194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Emotions can certainly be misleading: they can fool you into believing stuff that is definitely, demonstrably untrue. Yet emotions are also our indispensable tool for navigating, for feeling our way through, the much larger domain of stuff that isn\'t susceptible to proof or disproof, that isn\'t checkable against the physical universe."', '"Fool,Universe,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Despite the best efforts of apologists like William Lane Craig, the \'evidence\' for Christianity\'s truth is, in truth, not the kind that science will or should ever admit. We believers mean something different by the word: something that puts faith permanently in the category of irreproducible results."', '"Best,Faith,Science"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Self-awareness is not the same thing as self-approval, any more than imagination is the same thing as day-dreaming."', '"Imagination,More,Self-Awareness"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', 'Libraries are public treasuries. They\'re ways in which well-meaning societies leave the wealth of the past arranged A to Z so that anyone walking past can find it.', '"Past,Wealth,Walking"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', 'Anyone can be self-educated if they find the loose end of something to care about passionately.', '"Care,End,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"You don\'t have to become an investment banker as a way of demonstrating that education has worked for you. But librarians have to believe in the values of high culture. Not just high culture but middle culture, low culture, kinds of exciting eye-catching crap of all kinds. Everyone needs that."', '"Education,Culture,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"I want to know why I read as a child with such a frantic appetite, why I sucked the words off the page with such an edge of desperation."', '"Words,Know,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', 'It\'s always struck me as unfair that writing has so little sensation when it\'s going well.', '"Me,Always,Well"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"Why do I write? From selfishness. Because this state of liquefied, complex concentration, however faintly and dimly I\'m able to perceive it, is the greatest pleasure I know."', '"Know,Pleasure,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdda', '"If you\'re a believer, God is not a thought-experiment requiring a special sub-creation to be tried out in. He\'s an actual, er, actuality already, embedded in a necessary and true story about guilt, hope, and liberty. I don\'t want C. S. Lewis doing his resourceful best to render Him as a fabulous special effect."', '"Best,God,Hope"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', '"All things by immortal power. Near of far, to each other linked are, that thou canst not stir a flower without troubling of a star."', '"Power,Flower,Far"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', '"For we are born in other\'s pain, and perish in our own."', '"Pain,Born,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', 'Look for me in the nurseries of Heaven.', '"Death,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', 'An atheist is a man who believes himself an accident.', '"Man,Atheist,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', '"The devil doesn\'t know how to sing, only how to howl."', '"Devil,Know,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddb', 'And left the flushed print in a poppy there.', '"Poppy,Left,Print"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddc', '"God has two families of children on this earth, the once-born and the twice-born."', '"God,Children,Earth"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddc', '"I first began to read religious books at school, and especially the Bible, when I was eleven years old; and almost immediately commenced a habit of secret prayer."', '"Prayer,Habit,Bible"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddc', '"The active part of man consists of powerful instincts, some of which are gentle and continuous; others violent and short; some baser, some nobler, and all necessary."', '"Man,Gentle,Active"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddc', '"As to the war, while it is always thought rash to have any strong military convictions, I have always believed that if they would go straight to Sebastopol early in the season they would take it with little difficulty."', '"War,Always,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddd', 'Knowledge is never too dear.', '"Knowledge,Never,Dear"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddd', 'There is less danger in fearing too much than too little.', '"Too Much,Danger,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddd', 'See and keep silent.', '"See,Silent,Keep"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddd', '"I call God to witness that as a private person I have done nothing unbeseeming an honest man, nor, as I bear the place of a public man, have I done anything unworthy of my place."', '"God,Man,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fddd', 'There is nothing more dangerous than security.', '"Nothing,Security,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdde', 'The whole of the hydrogen on the earth might be transformed at once and the success of the experiment published at large to the universe as a new star.', '"Success,Universe,New"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdde', '"It has long been known that the chemical atomic weight of hydrogen was greater than one-quarter of that of helium, but so long as fractional weights were general there was no particular need to explain this fact, nor could any definite conclusions be drawn from it."', '"Long,Need,Explain"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdde', '"The cosmical importance of this conclusion is profound and the possibilities it opens for the future very remarkable, greater in fact than any suggested before by science in the whole history of the human race."', '"Science,Future,History"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I get so much inspiration from my travels, but I also started an exercise where I write down so many words every week. Then I begin crossing them off. We create a grid of words and also images, but words for me are more ample because you can interpret them your own way."', '"Me,Exercise,Words"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I\'m inspired by many things, from landscapes to textiles. Art and architecture always influence my design process."', '"Art,Architecture,Design"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I\'m so not interested in gossip. It just gives me the creeps. I love the work; I love what I do. If somebody sends me an interview that has any connotation of something that\'s not interesting or genuine, I\'m not interested. I really detach myself from it."', '"Love,Work,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"When a sketch comes into this three-dimensional form and everybody contributes, it\'s really fantastic."', '"Three-Dimensional,Sketch,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"Milan, for me, is a city of discovery. You can find some amazing gardens behind some great houses; I also love finding beautiful galleries and incredible shops, but you have to explore. And the food is amazing."', '"Love,Food,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"All the Tauruses I know have this connection to the earth and the environment. We are very curious people, very loyal, very aware of and respectful of our surroundings. Also, we\'re stubborn, but that\'s our way. We understand what we want, which is not bad."', '"Bad,Way,Connection"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I just hate people who are lazy. To be on my team, you have to have energy and a sense of wanting to learn. That really excites me."', '"Hate,Me,Energy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I drape a lot. I cut. I have to touch. For me, it\'s almost impossible to start without that."', '"Me,Impossible,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'I do go back to Brazil once a year. I miss my family.', '"Family,Back,Brazil"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I don\'t love reading so much, but I love book shopping."', '"Love,Shopping,Reading"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I hate to sound esoteric, but there is something about a house that leads you to that one chair, that one corner, where you just sit and feel comfortable."', '"Hate,Feel,Chair"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"Right after high school, I moved to Rio and took classes to become a technician for a manufacturing factory where you had to figure out how to produce 3,000 pairs of jeans. But in Rio, I was by myself, which was very liberating, being so young. I got to do my own thing."', '"Myself,School,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"My parents had a factory, so I was linked to the textile and fashion industry."', '"Parents,Fashion,Industry"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I wonder if I would have been less organic of a designer without my background. Maybe I would be more academic about designing, more methodical. I want things to be a certain way, and I\'m very precise, but school itself wasn\'t that relevant for me."', '"Me,Way,School"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"My mom, she was unbelievable. She ran the whole town. She was like the mayor. There would be 15 people eating at our lunch table. She\'d drag people from the street."', '"Mom,Lunch,Street"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I came to New York when I was 21, 22. I couldn\'t speak English. I knew I wanted to go to fashion school."', '"New,School,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I wanted to be involved with fashion, though I didn\'t know what being a designer meant."', '"Know,Fashion,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I hope the average woman feels she needs practicality but with a little bit of fantasy. Otherwise, it\'s just not fashion."', '"Hope,Woman,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'I\'m not an artist. I\'m a fashion designer of clothes.', '"Fashion,Clothes,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'I never liked sleeping; I always think I am missing something.', '"I Am,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I have no tolerance for boredom. I spend so many hours in the office, and I still love it."', '"Love,Tolerance,Boredom"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'I don\'t listen to music when designing. We create in silence. I go through a torturous process because everything has to be precise and right.', '"Music,Silence,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"People don\'t really go to museums in Rio. I shouldn\'t say it\'s not sophisticated, but, you know, they go to the beach."', '"People,Know,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"Rio was a period of my life, and then, poof, I\'m gone. I was very young living here, just kind of floating. New York was a foundation for everything I do today. Rio was the bridge."', '"Life,Today,Bridge"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"When people ask me what it is about Brazil and my work, it\'s not something that I can say literally. It\'s unidentifiable. It\'s like when you do research and things inspire you. If you\'re smart enough, then obviously you don\'t take it literally. The inspiration will come out later somehow."', '"Work,Me,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"Brazil is not what you see but what you feel. Once you spend time here - a week, two weeks - you get in the vibe. It\'s really intoxicating."', '"Time,Feel,See"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I cannot live without art: it excites me, it challenges me, and it leads me to the next thing."', '"Art,Me,Challenges"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I think the women that we dress, the women who buy our clothes, they have a certain strength. It could be about the clothes, it could be about themselves. It\'s just attractive."', '"Strength,Women,Dress"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"When I say art influences me, which it does, it\'s not at all in a literal form. You go and see exhibitions or collections or meet an artist. It\'s all a compilation. Every moment, at all times, all this information. Then all this information disappears, and it shows up later in the process."', '"Art,Moment,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"The bottom line is that red carpet helps us broaden the appeal of the brand. Calvin Klein used to be about a very specific woman, but we\'ve dressed so many different women at awards."', '"Women,Woman,Red"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'Each season I strive to design a forward-thinking and effortless collection with a very clean minimalist aesthetic.', '"Design,Aesthetic,Clean"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'My love of fashion stemmed from my mother\'s passion for it.', '"Love,Passion,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', 'I love to garden and cook whenever I get the chance and escape anywhere that\'s peaceful and quiet. My philosophy on living well is to always stay positive in life.', '"Positive,Life,Love"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"If you have beautiful knees, show your knees. I\'m not a puritan. I love skin."', '"Love,Beautiful,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"My mother was very fashion-oriented, and she started a little children\'s wear business that became large in this little town. She used to be able to look at a picture of an outfit and just start cutting the fabric right there."', '"Business,Look,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"I came to New York in 1986. My father didn\'t think it was a good idea. I didn\'t know how I found it, but I went to Hunter College. I had no money and I couldn\'t speak English."', '"Money,Good,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde1', '"You think 24-7 when you\'re a creative person. And I find pleasure in everything - if I\'m in a flea market, I\'m there on my downtime, but I\'m also there searching for the collection. I don\'t separate the two."', '"Person,Pleasure,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde6', '"In short, not only are things not what they seem, they are not even what they are called!"', '"Short,Things,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde6', '"We all wish to reach a ripe old age, but none of us are prepared to admit that we are already there."', '"Age,Old Age,Wish"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde2', 'I am responsible only to God and history.', '"God,History,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde2', 'The whole secret of the campaigns unleashed against Spain can be explained in two words: masonry and communism... we have to extirpate these two evils from our land.', '"Words,Communism,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde2', 'There will be no communism.', '"Will,Communism"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '\'Say Her Name\' was a book I never wanted to write and never expected to write. I wasn\'t trying to do anything except write a book for Aura - a book that I thought I had to write.', '"Name,Never,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"I have never liked the memoir form because I tend to think that memory fictionalizes anyway. Once you claim that you are writing a narrative purely from memory, you are already in the realm of fiction."', '"Memory,Never,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"When I see a blatant injustice, I can\'t keep quiet. I\'ve been that way since I was a little kid."', '"Way,See,Injustice"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"What\'s important about me is that I really have, in ways I never could have foreseen when I was young, a writing career that\'s reached a lot of different places."', '"Me,Important,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"I think the fact that my wife died in Mexico City makes it very important to me; my life went up in smoke at that moment, the family and the future we were going to have. At that point, I was anchored to the city in a way I\'ve never been anchored to a place before."', '"Life,Family,Future"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"My earliest memories of going to Fenway with my father are a blur: many games, me too young to care, but aware that our team \'stunk.\' In those years, the 1960s, the Red Sox baseball card I always coveted most was not Carl Yastrzemski\'s but the far more ordinary Felix Mantilla\'s."', '"Memories,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"The U.S., like any other country, allows tourists into its borders in order to make money off them, and there\'s nothing wrong with that. Why give out tourist visas if you\'re not going to let tourists be tourists?"', '"Money,Country,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"You witness a lot as a journalist, and what you witness becomes a part of you."', '"Witness,Journalist,Lot"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"In U.S. discourse, immigrants are mostly represented as less than human, a policy problem, or as just that, a category, and categories are prisons."', '"Policy,Human,Immigrants"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', 'My only way of processing anything for me is by writing.', '"Me,Way,Anything"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"I had one of those farcical bar mitzvahs where they spell out the words phonetically on index cards, and you don\'t even know what you\'re saying."', '"Words,Know,Cards"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde3', '"I identify myself as what I am. I\'m half Jewish, like Proust. I have no other way to put it."', '"Myself,I Am,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"Fantasy, abandoned by reason, produces impossible monsters; united with it, she is the mother of the arts and the origin of marvels."', '"Impossible,Fantasy,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"In art, there is no need for color; I see only light and shade. Give me a crayon, and I will paint your portrait."', '"Art,Me,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', 'I have now established myself in a most enviable manner. Those who require something of me must seek me out - I remain apart. I work for no one unless he is a high-ranking personality or a friend.', '"Work,Personality,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"Painting (like poetry) chooses from universals what is most apposite. It brings together, in a single imaginary being, circumstances and characteristics which occur in nature in many different persons."', '"Nature,Poetry,Together"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"I am beginning to have more powerful enemies and more envious ones, too."', '"I Am,Beginning,Enemies"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"I have just returned from Arenas and feel very tired. His Excellency loaded me with a thousand honours; I have painted his portrait and that of his wife and boy and girl with unexpected success, for other artists had been there previously and not been successful."', '"Success,Tired,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', 'I will give a proof to demonstrate with facts that there are no rules in painting and that oppression or servile obligation of making all study or follow the same path is a great impediment for the young who profess this very difficult art.', '"Art,Great,Path"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde4', '"With all my work, I have not more, with my shares in the bank and the Academy, than twelve or thirteen thousand reales a year, and with all this, I am as contented as the happiest man on earth."', '"Work,Man,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"In my long career I have experienced a lot, but never changed."', '"Long,Never,Career"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The people who know me know: I am a good guy with a big heart.', '"Good,Heart,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I could play for another club in Europe but my heart is beating too much for Bayern. But I could imagine going to the U.S., Qatar or Dubai for a new experience."', '"Experience,Heart,Dubai"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I\'ll never cheat.', '"Never,Cheat"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The scars in my face are the source of my strength.', '"Strength,Face,Scars"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"When I arrived, Bayern were sitting at 14th place in the Bundesliga and weren\'t in the Champions League. Twelve years later, I left with 23 titles."', '"Place,Sitting,Titles"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'It\'s always been that opponents get down to business against Bayern specifically because they want to show how desperate they are to defeat the champions.', '"Business,Always,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'If I am on the pitch there is a lot of energy in my body.', '"Energy,I Am,Body"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I deserved to win the Ballon d\'Or.', '"Win,Deserved"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"My 100th goal is good for me personally but above all, the team is very important."', '"Good,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I can imagine staying in Munich after the end of my career. I have bought a very nice house, I feel good here and I like the mentality."', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Bayen need quality, you have to invest and upgrade!"', '"Quality,Upgrade,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"To be honest, I have no idea what happens after my career."', '"Happens,No Idea,After"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"It\'s true - ever since I was born, I\'ve been through some tough situations. But that\'s what has given me the strength and the drive to succeed."', '"Strength,Me,Drive"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I just want to play for a competitive team that will offer me the best possible opportunity to win titles.', '"Best,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I really like the mentality of the people in Munich.', '"People,Mentality,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'It\'s important for me that I\'m able to walk around the city without being bothered all the time.', '"Time,Walk,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I really want to lift the Champions League trophy one day.', '"Day,Trophy,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I want to win as many titles as possible with Bayern Munich.', '"Win,Possible,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I am very motivated, I always want to play."', '"I Am,Always,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I hope to continue playing until the age of 40, just like Francesco Totti."', '"Hope,Age,Continue"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Serie A is a great tournament with many excellent players.', '"Great,Tournament,Players"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I want to give something new to this club, I want to bring Fiorentina into the top three of the table."', '"New,Three,Table"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Football is my life, I love it."', '"Life,Love,Football"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'You know that I played football because of the fun and to enjoy it.', '"Football,Fun,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"If you play well, then you make yourself a great name and the money comes on its own. You earn money for what you did."', '"Money,Great,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I do not just play for money.', '"Money,Play,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I have always given 100 per cent, power and performance."', '"Power,Performance,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"When you\'ve been Bayern for so long and it\'s your second home, moving away from here is not easy."', '"Home,Long,Easy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I\'ll always have a winning mentality in me, and I want to transmit that. I equally feel what the players are feeling and I know them as men."', '"Men,Me,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"When the locker room needing shaking up, I did it. I remained myself, a leader, until the end."', '"Myself,End,Room"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'One day I\'ll know what it\'s like to be a manager.', '"Day,Know,One Day"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The whole treble year under Jupp Heynckes was incredible.', '"Year,Incredible,Whole"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I am simply happy in Munich.', '"I Am,Happy,Simply"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I listen to my emotions. That\'s why I react once I get provoked sometimes.', '"Emotions,Sometimes,React"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I love playing for France and I feel pride every time I am called up for the team.', '"Love,Time,Pride"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"At Bayern, I have rediscovered the pleasure of playing. Here, my body is completely free."', '"Free,Body,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"If you play in the Champions League, it\'s a very special feeling, there\'s a different atmosphere."', '"Special,Atmosphere,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"In Europe, Bayern is my last club - 100 per cent."', '"Club,Europe,Last"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Maybe I\'ll quit after my time at Bayern; maybe I will play somewhere else for one more year.', '"Time,Will,Quit"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I am almost German now.', '"I Am,Now,Almost"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I am well aware of it myself that I have to be careful. But I want to make it clear that I am not a dirty player.', '"Myself,I Am,Dirty"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I don\'t have any problem with tackles or duels, but I react when I notice that someone is only trying to kick me out of the game. But I never have the intention to hurt anyone. Everything is forgotten again a minute later."', '"Me,Game,React"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I sometimes lose my calm for a moment, but only when I notice that an opponent is deliberately trying to injure me."', '"Moment,Me,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Bayern and I are like a married couple.', '"Like,Married Couple,Married"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Normally I provide a lot of assists and do a lot of dribbling - but it\'s always great when you score a goal.', '"Great,Always,Score"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'You know when you play in Leverkusen it is always a difficult game.', '"Game,Difficult,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'You have to be mentally strong to withstand the ridicule of other children and the stares of adults.', '"Children,Strong,Ridicule"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"This is my face, it is the one people know me to be. I am happy with my face. Why shouldn\'t I be happy?"', '"Face,Me,I Am Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I was the boy next door who always knew what it meant to have no money. That changed when I turned professional. I was crazy.', '"Money,Crazy,Door"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"In 2008 or 2009, every big club wanted me: Juventus, Inter, Milan, Barca, Real, Chelsea, Manchester."', '"Me,Real,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I will play until my knee, my ankle or my back say \'stop.\'"', '"Will,Back,Stop"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I have a really good relationship with Bayern. I might become a coach after retirement, but with the youth teams."', '"Relationship,Good,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'When I\'m on the pitch I always give everything for my team.', '"Always,Everything,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I always play with character.', '"Character,Always,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I know there are not a lot of players with my quality in this world.', '"World,Quality,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"It is no secret that Louis van Gaal and I did not get along. But for me personally, the matter is closed and forgotten."', '"Me,Matter,Secret"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I am very happy in Munich and my family is totally settled - and now I have a son who is a genuine Bavarian.', '"Family,I Am,Genuine"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"If I decide to leave Bayern Munich, it will be for a Spanish club. I have to think about what my family wants as well and my wife would be delighted to move to Spain. She doesn\'t like all the rain and snow and is reluctant to go to England."', '"Family,Rain,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I won everything I could win with Bayern and individually.', '"Win,Everything,Won"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"We are Bayern. We have the highest standards, and always want to win everything, so the Champions League is a very big target."', '"Win,Big,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"No one\'s saying anything against healthy, fair hardness. That\'s a part of football. But referees must look more closely and make sure limits are not exceeded."', '"Football,Look,Limits"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I can be used in various positions.', '"I Can,Used,Positions"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I\'ve just got better as a player thanks to Pep.', '"Better,Thanks,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Each and every player wants to win every game, but that\'s simply not possible."', '"Game,Win,Possible"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'We have to play as a team every game.', '"Game,Play,Team"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I think every club in the world would like to have David Alaba.', '"World,Club,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Lionel Messi, without hesitation! I\'d love to play with him and Xavi."', '"Love,Play,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Obviously, there are many clubs that make me dream, like Real Madrid or Barcelona."', '"Me,Real,Dream"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"My son Saif was born here, he may even one day play for Germany."', '"Day,Son,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"My eldest daughter Hiziya always makes fun of my German, and I laugh with her. I did not learn the language in school, but in my daily life, from other people."', '"Life,Daily,Fun"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I feel rejected in France. And do you know why I signed for Bayern when I could have gone anywhere? Because they made me feel wanted.', '"Me,Feel,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I am emotional, but that\'s not a negative."', '"I Am,Negative,Emotional"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Ancelotti is a champion, in all respects."', '"Champion,Respects"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'People are so quick to say someone is a fantastic player and deserves to win the Ballon d\'Or after just one good year. I disagree with that.', '"Good,People,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"For me, you have to prove yourself over 10, 12 or 15 years if you want to be among the best. Do that and then I will congratulate you."', '"Best,Me,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I\'m very strong mentally. I have a lot of character. I never give in; I always have the drive to keep going and to work hard to achieve my goals.', '"Work,Keep Going,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Bayern offers the young guys a huge opportunity.', '"Opportunity,Young,Huge"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I appreciate every guy, whether he is a footballer or a cook."', '"Footballer,Guy,He"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"There is Messi, and then the rest."', '"Rest,Messi,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I am dreaming of winning the treble again. I will never forget how I felt after winning it in 2012-13. It was like we were flying. It\'s a great feeling, it\'s utter madness. I definitely want to have that feeling again at some stage of my career."', '"Great,I Am,Winning"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The 4-1-4-1 system is weird.', '"Weird,System"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I\'ve experienced so many emotions with Bayern.', '"Emotions,Many,Experienced"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The Bayern jersey means so much to me.', '"Me,Means,Jersey"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I like to create a good atmosphere in the dressing room.', '"Good,Create,Room"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'The Ballon d\'Or doesn\'t interest me any more.', '"Me,More,Interest"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I have to train in order to be happy.', '"Happy,Be Happy,Train"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Bayern will always have a place in my heart and what I need, I can accomplish here."', '"Heart,Will,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I feel very comfortable in Munich and my family is doing well.', '"Family,Feel,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"People would say: \'Look what he has on his face, look at his head. What is this scar? It\'s so ugly.\' Wherever I went, people would look at me. And not because I was a good person or because my name is Franck or was a good footballer, but because of the scar."', '"Good,Look,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I\'m not afraid of anything.', '"Anything,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Guardiola knows that the little details that can make us better. He analyses the game instantly - that\'s his biggest strength, his best characteristic."', '"Best,Strength,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"Ronaldo certainly scores goals, but I do too. He certainly scores more than I do, but we don\'t have the same style."', '"Goals,Style,More"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'Everyone knows that I had a lot of good coaches but one person was very important: Jupp Heynckes.', '"Good,Important,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'My relationship with the fans has always been incredible.', '"Relationship,Fans,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'He does great things on the pitch but the coach Van Gaal was a bad man.', '"Great,Man,Bad"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"For me, Munich is more than just a second home. I can imagine staying forever."', '"Home,Me,I Can"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', 'I think everyone knows I\'m better on the left side.', '"Better,Everyone,Side"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"I never said I wanted to move to Real Madrid. If I did, I would have said so publicly."', '"Real,Never,Said"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde7', '"In truth, there is nobody who will be able to play like Zidane."', '"Truth,Will,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"Halfway through the decade, we realized that we had a great team and that we could do great things, and that we could probably have something here that we believed we had a chance to reach greatness."', '"Great,Chance,Greatness"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"Where Joe was more vocal and emotional whereas Chuck was very reserved. But, both of them executed great strategy and both of them demanded a lot of their players."', '"Great,Strategy,More"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"I really don\'t look at comparing things that way because even in a 14-game season, there could be a running back who could have a lot more carries than other running backs."', '"Look,Way,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"And so, it\'s not a thing of how many carries, but were you effective when you did carry."', '"Carry,Did,How"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"Yes, I would have rather finished up in Pittsburgh."', '"Up,Finished,Rather"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"After 12 years, the old butterflies came back. Well, I guess at my age you call them moths."', '"Age,Back,Old"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', 'It\'s not how you come out of the starting blocks.', '"Come,How,Blocks"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"But, as always, Mr. Rooney would come over and shake your hand and congratulate you on a good game, no matter what the situation was."', '"Good,Game,Situation"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"And, coaching has never been an option for me."', '"Me,Never,Coaching"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', 'All I wanted to be was a player.', '"Wanted,Player"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', 'The Houston Astrodome was kind of a tough field.', '"Tough,Field,Houston"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde8', '"Jack Lambert is mean and relentless wherever he goes, on and off the field! I do remember many times he would chase me in practice but no way would I let him catch me."', '"Me,Remember,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde9', '"Economists agree about economics - and that\'s a science - and they disagree about economic policy because that\'s a value judgment... I\'ve had profound disagreements on policy with the famous Milton Friedman. But, on economics, we agree."', '"Science,Famous,Value"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde9', '"With the danger of war, there is a danger that the economy will go down."', '"War,Will,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde9', 'I am a believer in cooperation.', '"I Am,Cooperation,Believer"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde9', 'People confuse economists and economic policy.', '"People,Policy,Economists"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fde9', '"The immediate effect of the deficit is to make you feel good, like when you go on a trip and pay later. You feel good, and then you get a hangover. The deficit makes you feel good - until you pay later."', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdea', '"I don\'t say I create. I copy, of course. I\'ve never been interested in the point of view of the tailor or creator. Fashion is a visual impression. This is why I often refuse the name of fashion designer. It\'s a superficial, stupid job. The social-psychological aspect is more interesting."', '"Stupid,View,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdea', 'Good taste doesn\'t exist. It is our taste. We have to be proud of it.', '"Good,Proud,Taste"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdea', 'The reason I do this job is because I started to be a painter. Making money in art was difficult. The easiest way to make money was to use art for some other reason. One of the easiest and most interesting from an economic point of view was fashion. Fashion pays.', '"Money,Art,View"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdea', 'I was in love with Lagerfeld\'s designs.', '"Love,Designs"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'I studied at the Piccolo Teatro di Milano; I was a theatre actor.', '"Theatre,Actor,Studied"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'Left love behind many years ago. Now it rests under a cross in the cemetery in Tombstone.', '"Love,Behind,Cemetery"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'You\'re the one who likes cigars right? Try smoking this.', '"Smoking,Right,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'It doesn\'t matter. What matters is that you\'re about to die.', '"Die,Matter,Matters"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', '"If you\'re a big Hollywood star, you make one movie a year at the most. I can make five in Europe."', '"Big,I Can,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'Someone who was a part of my life. Probably the only one that really mattered.', '"Life,My Life,Someone"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', 'Every western I did and will do; I will do it for the never ending young kid inside of me.', '"Me,Ending,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', '"I\'m crazy about westerns. I need to do a western once in a while. It\'s like you know, eating bread, eating pasta, drinking wine. It\'s in my blood. I need it."', '"Crazy,Eating,Pasta"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', '"I could be a star and maybe make lots of money, or I could change roles all the time and have a more interesting - and longer - career."', '"Change,Money,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', '"Everyone has a first love, and mine was the western. When I was a child and dreamed of the movies, it was always as a cowboy on a white horse."', '"Love,Movies,White"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdeb', '"There were many, many other \'Django\' films following mine, with other actors and directors, but there is only one \'Django.\'"', '"Mine,Only,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"I just go wherever work brings me. I share a house with friends in L.A., and I share a house with friends in Montreal when I\'m there."', '"Work,Me,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"As an actor, as much as I\'m interested in how you make movies and TV shows, even as a kid, I\'ve always hated making of featurettes and special features on DVDs. I think it breaks the spell."', '"Movies,Always,Special"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"I watched \'E.T.\' when I was a kid every day. Well, not all of it every day; I\'d pause it and start over again. But I\'ve watched \'E.T.\' about 400 times in my life."', '"Life,My Life,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"The first play that I saw was \'Cyrano,\' and I remember going home - I was like nine years old - and trying to learn the monologues."', '"Home,Remember,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"I didn\'t act professionally before going to drama school. I don\'t know if I had the confidence. I didn\'t think I\'d get in when I first auditioned for drama school, and then I did."', '"Confidence,Drama,School"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"I\'m not sure I\'ll find acting satisfying creatively forever. If you get the good roles, it\'s great - if you have the freedom to choose your projects and not just do anything and everything."', '"Freedom,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', 'I think there comes a point in probably most father-son relationships where the son kind of starts becoming the parent.', '"Son,Point,Parent"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"Today, the Pope is only a religious figure. At the time of \'The Borgias,\' he was also a political leader, a financial leader, and the head of an army. I think popes are much less relevant today than they were then."', '"Time,Today,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdec', '"I started studying theater in school, and then I got into drama school at, like, 19, and it was a national drama school in Montreal, and so it was just you and nine other students for three years, and it was really intense."', '"Drama,School,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fded', 'I\'m an actor who isn\'t fond of dialogue and who loves to act silently.', '"Act,Dialogue,Actor"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fded', '"I think that in France, we really admire American films, we admire their drive, we admire the modernity and ellipsism in the film and the writing and the style of acting, and we look at them perhaps in a way to see what we can steal from them, too, to make our own films more modern."', '"Look,Drive,Style"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fded', '"What\'s interesting for me is that I generally consider myself to be more of a physical actor, and I\'m somebody that doesn\'t really want to use the dialogue but prefers to act through my body, and then sometimes when I have a script, I look and kind of throw away the dialogue and I just look at how I can expressive it through my body."', '"Myself,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fded', '"I think there\'s a kind of love relationship between an actor and an audience, and this is something I really feel with the audiences in France."', '"Love,Relationship,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe01', 'Our days and nights have sorrows woven with delights.', '"Days,Delights,Woven"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe01', '"To will what God doth will, that is the only science that gives us any rest."', '"God,Science,Rest"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', 'I know the Haitian people - because I am the Haitian people.', '"I Am,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', '"It is not a question of whether I believe in voodoo. I am a scholar and, as such, I have studied the concept of voodoo. I have created the faculty of Afro-Haitian ethnology in our university where the concept of voodoo is taught. Voodoo is not superstition. It is a philosophy, a conception of God."', '"God,Believe,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', 'The chief of the tribe is supposed to be the father of all people of the tribe. That is the Haitian way.', '"Father,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', 'The people of Haiti have always called me Papa Doc. I was first their doctor. Now I am also their president for life.', '"Life,Doctor,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', 'I am the Haitian flag. He who is my enemy is the enemy of the fatherland.', '"I Am,Enemy,Flag"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdee', '"As revolutionary, I have no right to disregard the voice of the people."', '"People,Voice,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"Gravitational and electromagnetic interactions are long-range interactions, meaning they act on objects no matter how far they are separated from each other."', '"Matter,Meaning,Act"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', 'I feel squeezed like a lemon - interviewers and people keep turning up unannounced at my office!', '"Feel,People,Up"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"Fundamental research is needed to make progress, which you cannot do solely by copying others. If you only do applied research, you quickly lose creativity."', '"Progress,Lose,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"In 1955, I got my degree in electrical-mechanical engineering. I realised, however, that my interest was less in practical applications than in the understanding of the underlying theoretical structure, and I decided to learn physics."', '"Understanding,Physics,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"As an assistant in the polytechnic department, I was able to finance new studies and got my Physics Masters Degree in 1958 and my Ph.D. in 1959."', '"Finance,New,Physics"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"I was born in Belgium on 6 November 1932. I am married to Mira Nikomarow and have five children: Michele, Anne, Georges, from a first marriage with Esther Dujardin, and Sarah, Helene from a second one with Danielle Vindal."', '"Marriage,I Am,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"My parents emigrated from Poland in 1924 with my brother, who was a few months old. They were from a simple family of Polish Jews. They were looking, I suppose, for a better economic life and were escaping from an anti-Semitic environment."', '"Life,Family,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', 'It\'s not necessary to have read everything about a particular subject in order to get interested in it. The main thing is to sort out what\'s important and what is peripheral in order to be able to dive in.', '"Important,Everything,Dive"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', 'The curiosity of the human mind is essential if you want citizens who think rather than accept the first nonsense they come to.', '"Mind,Curiosity,Accept"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdef', '"I like to call it the scalar boson because this reflects an essential component of the theory - it means that the field the boson travels through has no preferred direction, unlike the way a magnetic field does."', '"Direction,Way,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"All wars are civil wars, because all men are brothers."', '"War,Men,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"Genuine good taste consists in saying much in few words, in choosing among our thoughts, in having order and arrangement in what we say, and in speaking with composure."', '"Good,Communication,Thoughts"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"A good historian is timeless; although he is a patriot, he will never flatter his country in any respect."', '"Respect,Good,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', 'All earthly delights are sweeter in expectation than in enjoyment; but all spiritual pleasures more in fruition than in expectation.', '"Spiritual,More,Enjoyment"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"Had we not faults of our own, we should take less pleasure in complaining of others."', '"Pleasure,Own,Complaining"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"Exactness and neatness in moderation is a virtue, but carried to extremes narrows the mind."', '"Mind,Moderation,Virtue"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', 'Nothing is more despicable than a professional talker who uses his words as a quack uses his remedies.', '"Words,Nothing,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', 'If we were faultless we should not be so much annoyed by the defects of those with whom we associate.', '"Annoyed,Those,Much"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"There is a set of religious, or rather moral, writings which teach that virtue is the certain road to happiness, and vice to misery in this world. A very wholesome and comfortable doctrine, and to which we have but one objection, namely, that it is not true."', '"Happiness,World,True"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"Do not make best friends with a melancholy sad soul. They always are heavily loaded, and you must bear half."', '"Best,Sad,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', '"Children are excellent observers, and will often perceive your slightest defects. In general, those who govern children, forgive nothing in them, but everything in themselves."', '"Children,Nothing,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf0', 'Little opportunities should be improved.', '"Little,Opportunities,Should"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf1', '"In order to consolidate the euro we need to harmonise our economic, fiscal and social policies, hence we are going toward greater integration."', '"Need,Order,Social"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf1', 'Great Britain is not part of the euro-zone; but the decision we take will have great importance for Great Britain.', '"Great,Decision,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf1', 'We need to put in place an economic system of governance for the euro-zone.', '"Place,Governance,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf1', 'The Europeans must now honor their commitments. That is the position that France is defending.', '"Honor,Position,Now"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf1', 'France does not practice revenge.', '"Revenge,Practice,France"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', '"I started writing and photographing for different publications and finally ended up being the correspondent in South Asia, for the Geneva-based Journal de Geneve, which at one time used to be one of the best international newspapers in Europe."', '"Best,Time,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', 'The West remains obsessed by the caste system.', '"Caste,System,West"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', 'I was born in Paris in 1950. I had a strict upper-class Catholic education but I never really fitted in the system and revolted against it quite early.', '"Education,Never,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', '"I have no intention of going back to France, except for yearly visits to meet my family."', '"Family,Back,Meet"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', '"I have an interest in spirituality, and it opens up so many different areas of Indian life."', '"Life,Indian,Interest"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf2', '"Being married to a daughter of India is a natural complement of my being in this country for 30 years. My roots are very much in this country, even though I remain a Westerner."', '"Country,Roots,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We have chased away the clouds, the sky is all \'rose.\'"', '"Sky,Clouds,Rose"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The fight against global warming is a humanitarian issue - how the planet can be preserved - and it is also an issue of considerable economic importance, of what we call green growth."', '"Growth,Green,Fight"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The transatlantic relationship is vital for both our countries: France will remain a reliable ally of the United States. Nevertheless, ally does not mean aligned."', '"Relationship,Will,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Nothing was given to me, nothing was entrusted to me, nothing was assigned to me. Everything I have, I took by right."', '"Me,Nothing,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I am not deaf. I hear the anger. I see the dissatisfaction, and I have to go faster."', '"Anger,I Am,See"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'There\'s always a risk when the candidate becomes president: Will he deliver what is expected of him?', '"Will,Always,Deliver"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'My adversary is the world of finance.', '"Finance,World,Adversary"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I commit myself to serve my country.', '"Myself,Country,Serve"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Long live the Republic, and long live France."', '"Long,Live,Republic"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Each country has a soul, and France\'s soul is equality."', '"Equality,Soul,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Though Africa is not responsible for emitting greenhouse gases, it is suffering the consequences of climate change."', '"Change,Suffering,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'People need to see signs of equal treatment across society.', '"Society,People,See"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I don\'t like indecent, unearned wealth. But it is legitimate for an entrepreneur who has created something to make a good living."', '"Good,Wealth,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'There cannot be any concessions on the matter of human rights or the criteria for visa liberalisation.', '"Matter,Human Rights,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Be happy, be proud, be generous, be respectful, be proud to be French citizens."', '"Happy,Proud,Be Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Everyone says Francois Mitterrand had huge charisma. But before he was president they used to call him badly dressed, old, archaic and say he knew nothing about the economy... until the day he was elected. It\'s called universal suffrage. When you\'re elected, you become the person that embodies France."', '"Day,Nothing,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France, because it was attacked cowardly, shamelessly, violently, France will be merciless against the barbarians of Daesh."', '"Will,Because,Against"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We must not lose time, neither for dealing in a suitable way with the question of the United Kingdom\'s exit, nor for providing a new impetus for the E.U."', '"Time,Lose,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The migrant question is directly linked to the crisis in Syria and Iraq.', '"Crisis,Question,Migrant"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"When I took part in European leaders summits, it was sometimes unpleasant for me to hear Romanian, Polish, Portuguese, and Italian friends speak English, although I admit that on an informal basis, first contacts can be made in this language. Nevertheless, I will defend everywhere the use of the French language."', '"Me,Sometimes,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"A jolt is necessary. Europe must reaffirm it values of freedom, solidarity, peace. The EU must be understood and controlled by its citizens. I will do everything to secure profound change rather than decline."', '"Change,Freedom,Peace"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Not in the constitution, but I would propose a law to the French parliament that provides for reducing the budget deficit year by year, until we have reached a balanced budget by 2017."', '"Law,Parliament,Constitution"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I want to initiate a change in society in the long term.', '"Change,Society,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Whoever pays should control; whoever pays should sanction. I agree. But budgetary union should be completed by a partial mutualisation of debts through eurobonds.', '"Control,Through,Agree"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I am proud to have been capable of giving people hope again.', '"Hope,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I don\'t want to drive the markets crazy. I don\'t want to create trouble, but rather order and rules and norms. We have to struggle against financial excesses, those who speculate with sovereign debt, those who develop financial products which have done so much harm."', '"Struggle,Drive,Crazy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"My obligation, if I become president, is to give another direction to Europe than the one that is being forced upon us today."', '"Today,Direction,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"What the French want is coherence, stability and justice. If I am in a favorable position today, it\'s because my fellow citizens want to make the effort to straighten out the country, and at the same time they want it to be just and equitable."', '"Time,Today,Justice"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I am the president of the youth of France.', '"Youth,I Am,President"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"There is just one France... one single nation, united in the same destiny."', '"Destiny,Nation,Same"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The British have been particularly shy about the issues of financial regulation, and attentive only to the interests of the City - hence their reluctance to see the introduction of a tax on financial transactions and tax harmonisation in Europe."', '"City,Shy,See"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I am attached to the French language. I will defend the ubiquitous use of French.', '"I Am,Will,Language"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Before you, I engage myself to serve my country with the devotion and the exemplary that this post demands. I understand responsibilities of the job and, as such, I give a republican salute to Nicolas Sarkozy who has led France for 5 years and who deserves all of our respect."', '"Respect,Myself,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Austerity need not be Europe\'s fate.', '"Fate,Europe,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"That is now my mission: to provide a European vision of growth, employment, prosperity - in one word, our future."', '"Future,Vision,Growth"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Is France a northern European export powerhouse, or a Mediterranean indebted and dependent economy? Yes to both."', '"Mediterranean,Export,Economy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I gave myself an objective, to be the second president from Correze and finally to be the successor to Francois Mitterrand."', '"Myself,Finally,President"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France, after the month of May, will share trust with the current leadership of the United States which, on many subjects, has tended to take useful positions in our view."', '"Leadership,Trust,View"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Nicolas Sarkozy said he could see a wave rising. For once he was right. The wave\'s coming; it\'s high, its strong, and it\'s going to smack him in the face."', '"Face,See,Rising"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I won\'t wait until the end of my term to say I made mistakes at the beginning. That\'s too late. I will try to adopt the proper behaviour, if the French give me the chance, right from the start."', '"Chance,Me,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"As a president I will be like the candidate that I am, a respectful candidate, a rallying candidate, a normal candidate for a normal presidency, at the service of the Republic."', '"Service,I Am,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I could have made a fortune in cheeseburgers, but I finally chose politics."', '"Politics,Fortune,Finally"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"My real adversary has no name, no face, no party. It will never be elected, yet it governs - the adversary is the world of finance."', '"Finance,Face,World"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"My dear citizens, fellow citizens, French people, this 6th of May, have just chosen change by bringing me the presidency of the French republic. I feel the honor, which has been given to me and the task, the important task faced beyond - in front of you to serve my country."', '"Change,Me,Honor"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I\'m going to gather all the French people who want change.', '"Change,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We are near, very near, to an end to the eurozone crisis... The worst - in the sense of the fear of the eurozone breaking up - is over. But the best isn\'t there yet."', '"Best,Fear,End"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We\'re all taking part in this solidarity. The French, the Germans, just like all the Europeans in the ESM. Let\'s stop thinking that there\'s only one country who\'s going to pay for the others. That\'s false."', '"Thinking,Country,Solidarity"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I would like a UK fully engaged in Europe, but I can\'t decide in place of the British. I see that for the moment they want to be more in retreat."', '"Moment,See,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France is the bridge between northern Europe and southern Europe. I refuse any division. If Europe has been reunified, it\'s not for it to then fall into egotism or \'each for one\'s own\'. Our duty is to set common rules around the principles of responsibility and solidarity."', '"Responsibility,Bridge,Duty"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Between France and Senegal there\'s a history. There\'s a language that we both speak. There\'s a culture that we share and to which both of our peoples have contributed. But beyond our history, beyond our language, beyond the links that have united us for so long, what unites us today is the future."', '"Future,History,Today"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"What is happening in the Sahel for the past several months is that terrorists have structured themselves, have installed themselves. It\'s not simply a menace for west Africa."', '"Past,Africa,Simply"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"An education program is, by definition, a societal program. Work should be done at school, rather than at home."', '"Education,Work,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We find ourselves in a difficult situation in Europe. There\'s a crisis, weak growth, unemployment... my duty is to ensure that by the end of my mandate France is in a better state than it was at the beginning."', '"Growth,Difficult,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"During a term in office there are highs and lows, but what counts is that the goal is set as well as the means to achieve it, and the force we put into getting results."', '"Achieve,Well,Results"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France isn\'t just any country in Europe, and its president is not an ordinary leader in the world. Sometimes directing or leading the way is not enough, he has to initiate policies, as Nicolas Sarkozy was able to demonstrate during his term."', '"World,Way,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I perfectly understood President Obama\'s attitude throughout the French presidential campaign. He had no reason to distance himself from Nicolas Sarkozy. It\'s the basic solidarity that leaders who worked together owe to each other.', '"Attitude,Together,Solidarity"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I want the French people to respect values that allow each individual to practice his or her faith, but in the frame of our common rules of secularism."', '"Faith,Respect,Practice"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'One thing that makes France different from other countries is the tradition of social solidarity. People from all backgrounds and political positions are willing to contribute for services and protection of society as a whole - but on the condition that money is being spent effectively and that everyone is paying their part.', '"Money,Society,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Europe needs an engine, and the Franco-German motor has provided that when the two nations have converged on important topics during critical periods. But that partnership shouldn\'t be a directorate for other EU members."', '"Important,Two,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We need the help of other member countries and leaders who, like us, want to see a change in Europe\'s direction. That\'s also my logic when I tell voters that electing me president will not only shape France\'s future, but also initiate change across all of Europe."', '"Change,Future,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'My goal is to put France back on its feet. I have to put this country back on its feet.', '"Feet,Country,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I don\'t want to leave my successor and my children to pay for France\'s debt.', '"Children,Leave,Debt"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We are a big country, with lots of advantages and history. We are proud to be French. We have to call on patriotism at this time... to ask for an effort in the battle against debt."', '"History,Time,Patriotism"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I know where I\'m going and I have told the French. I am sure if hope is there, we will be able to put France back on its feet... to live better in five years than we do today."', '"Hope,Today,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I think that France has not made it clear enough recently to our German friends how important it is to introduce euro bonds as a tool against speculation. And how the necessary budget discipline needs to be accompanied by growth.', '"Growth,Discipline,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I don\'t want euro bonds that serve to mutualize the entire debt of the countries in the euro zone. That can only work in the longer-term. I want euro bonds to be used to finance targeted investments in future-oriented growth projects. It isn\'t the same thing. Let\'s call them \'project bonds\' instead of euro bonds.', '"Work,Finance,Growth"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"If I become president, France will not continue with the same policies as under Nicolas Sarkozy - both in domestic policy and in foreign and European policy."', '"Will,Continue,Policy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"In an election, one needs both hope and audacity."', '"Hope,Election,Needs"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I am for a clear distinction between public and private life. I believe private matters should be regulated in private and I have asked those close to me to respect this.', '"Life,Respect,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I have defended the interests of France at the G8 in Washington; afterwards I was at Chicago to announce the withdrawal of French troops from Afghanistan; I have participated in two European summits, so I have fully respected the engagements I made to the French."', '"Two,Afghanistan,Made"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"My mission is to put France back on its feet. The priority is employment. Efforts have to be made, but those efforts must be made fairly."', '"Feet,Back,Mission"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I attach the greatest importance to an amplification of the peace efforts in the Middle East. I would also like to see a greater dialogue between the U.S. and the EU.', '"Peace,See,Dialogue"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The United Nations will be at the heart of our international activities. France will assume its full responsibilities at the Security Council by putting its status at the service of peace, respect for human rights and development."', '"Respect,Peace,Heart"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"To be influential in tomorrow\'s world, to defend our values and our development model, France needs Europe and Europe needs France."', '"Tomorrow,World,Development"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The British people have decided to leave. It is a sad decision but one which I respect. The vote puts the European Union in difficulties. It must recognise its shortfalls.', '"Respect,Sad,Decision"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Doesn\'t everyone have their hair done?', '"Hair,Done,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I do not like the rich.', '"Rich,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Sport allows people to come together, but politics divides people."', '"Politics,Together,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I support the French team - I go to all their matches - but I don\'t want to use sport for politics. That\'s not good for sport or for politics.', '"Politics,Good,Support"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The arguments in the Brexit vote and in the American presidential campaign are about the same. In a friendly way, may I also give some advice to the American people to make the right choice when the moment comes."', '"Moment,Advice,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I bow down in memory of the victims, and I come to tell my Armenian friends that we will never forget the tragedies that your people has endured."', '"Never Forget,Memory,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France is no longer herself when she is folded in on herself, tormented by ignorance and intolerance. The country would plunge into decline if it refused to be itself, if it was afraid of the future, afraid of the world."', '"Future,World,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The world owes an ecological debt to the African continent.', '"World,Debt,African"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'It is intolerable that in our country citizens should feel so upset and under assault because of their religious choice that they would conclude that they have to hide.', '"Feel,Choice,Country"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Transatlantic links are very important.', '"Important,Links,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The Republic will not be destroyed by terrorism.', '"Will,Terrorism,Republic"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The Republic will destroy terrorism.', '"Will,Terrorism,Destroy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Europe existed before Britain joined it.', '"Europe,Before,Existed"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I hope Britain stays in the European Union, but I don\'t want to decide for the British."', '"Hope,Decide,European Union"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I can understand countries don\'t want to join the euro, but they cannot impede the consolidation and strengthening of the eurozone."', '"I Can,Understand,Join"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"If Europe does not advance, it will fall or even be wiped out from the world map... My duty is to bring Europe out of its lethargy."', '"World,Duty,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I can\'t separate the fight with terrorism and the fight against global warming. These are two big global challenges we have to face up to because we have to leave our children more than a world free of terror; we also owe them a planet protected from catastrophes.', '"Fight,Face,Challenges"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'A country outside the euro zone cannot have a veto over countries in the euro zone.', '"Country,Outside,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Muslims in France should be able to practice their religion freely and safely.', '"Religion,Practice,Able"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I\'ve got a thick skin.', '"Skin,Thick Skin,Thick"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I don\'t know if you can hear me, but I have heard you. I heard your willingness to change. Your force, your hope... and I want to tell you how grateful I am. Thank you, thank you, thank you, people of France."', '"Change,Hope,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Everyone must understand that you can\'t demand solidarity when there\'s a problem and shirk your duties when there are solutions.', '"Solidarity,Everyone,Understand"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France wants Britain to remain in the E.U.; indeed, how can we imagine that friendly nation that is our ally and played a role on the international stage could be outside the E.U.?"', '"Stage,Nation,Outside"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"If the discussion centres on the essential principle of the E.U., the free movement of people and the ability to make decisions together, in that case, we don\'t want treaty change."', '"Change,Together,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"If there is not a united policy, this mechanism will not work: it will collapse, and it will... undoubtedly be the end of Schengen, the return of national borders."', '"Work,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I will not give way because too many previous governments have backed down.', '"Way,Will,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I prefer that people remember me as a president who made reforms rather than a president who did nothing.', '"Me,Remember,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I ask to be judged on the issue of unemployment.', '"Unemployment,Ask,Issue"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'A compromise appears out of reach on the stripping of terrorists\' nationality.', '"Compromise,Reach,Nationality"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Islamist terrorism has declared war against us, against France, Europe, the entire world."', '"War,World,Terrorism"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'France needs to improve training and education and the level of skills of its workforce.', '"Education,Training,Needs"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The real threat comes from terrorism.', '"Real,Terrorism,Threat"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"When we live longer, we must work a little bit longer."', '"Work,Live,Little Bit"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'It\'s not for Germany to decide for the rest of Europe.', '"Rest,Europe,Decide"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"My security is assured everywhere, and at any moment."', '"Moment,Security,Everywhere"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"When I travel officially... and when I travel on a private basis, I have protection that is less suffocating. But I am protected everywhere."', '"Travel,I Am,Protection"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Everyone must be in the same competitive situation, including on the fiscal level."', '"Situation,Everyone,Competitive"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'China... has the capacity to ensure its stability and growth.', '"Growth,Stability,China"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The extremists wanted to divide France; it came together.', '"Together,Divide,Extremists"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'There must be protection of the external borders.', '"Protection,Must,Borders"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"To resolve the climate crisis, good will, statements of intent are not enough. We are at breaking point."', '"Good,Will,Climate"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Our enemy in Syria is Daesh: it\'s not about containing but destroying this organisation.', '"Enemy,About,Our"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"ISIL struck France because it is \'free\' and \'the nation of human rights\'. This is not a war of civilisation, as these assassins don\'t have any. This is a war against the jihadist menace that threatens not just France."', '"War,Free,Nation"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Daesh is the enemy of Europe, and Europe cannot live with the idea that the crises that surround it don\'t have an effect on it."', '"Live,Enemy,Europe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Very strong declarations were made by those countries who are most responsible for global warming... the United States and China, which undertook commitments towards changing the situation."', '"Situation,Global Warming,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Make no mistake: we will win, and groups like ISIL will lose."', '"Lose,Mistake,Win"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Europe must be understood and controlled by its citizens.', '"Europe,Must,Understood"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Europe must act quickly where it\'s needed and must, once and for all, let member states handle what is their exclusive domain."', '"Act,Europe,Handle"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'I noticed that parts of the opposition have been hostile to any revision of the constitution.', '"Constitution,Opposition,Revision"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'There must be pressure on Moscow so that we have negotiations. Moscow will not succeed by unilaterally backing Bashar al-Assad.', '"Pressure,Will,Succeed"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'We must do everything to ensure that the Euro 2016 is a success.', '"Success,Everything,Must"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'We want the United Kingdom to remain in the European Union.', '"Kingdom,European Union,Want"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"France has been struck on the day of her national holiday - the 14th of July, Bastille Day - the symbol of liberty, because human rights are denied by fanatics, and France is clearly their target."', '"Day,July,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'We will continue to hit those who threaten us.', '"Will,Continue,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Calling into question the Touquet deal on the pretext that Britain has voted for Brexit and will have to start negotiations to leave the union doesn\'t make sense.', '"Start,Will,Leave"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The concept of the terrorists is to plunge our country into division.', '"Country,Division,Concept"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We are absolutely clear: when these unaccompanied minors have a family link in the United Kingdom, then they must go to the United Kingdom. And they must go quickly and in an efficient fashion."', '"Family,Fashion,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Being in the European Union has its advantages, and I think that is what the British are beginning to understand, what those who are tempted by the Brexit are going to reflect upon."', '"Beginning,Understand,Brexit"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Faced with terror, France must be strong, it must be great, and the state authorities must be firm."', '"Great,Be Strong,Strong"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'What the terrorists want is to scare us and fill us with dread.', '"Us,Want,Fill"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'My policies are producing results and will produce even more.', '"Will,More,Results"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Things are going better: there is more growth, less deficit, more competitiveness, better margins for companies, more purchasing power for workers."', '"Power,Growth,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Our biggest threat is not too much Europe, but too little."', '"Too Much,Europe,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Our common responsibility is to put Europe\'s interests first.', '"Responsibility,Europe,First"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The best thing the Democrats can do is to get Hillary Clinton elected.', '"Best,Get,Democrats"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Whatever happened during the French presidential campaign will leave no hard feelings. I perfectly understand why Angela Merkel supported Nicolas Sarkozy because of the action they have taken together, even though I have questioned its results, and because of their shared political sensibility."', '"Together,Political,Action"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"As much as I believe in the Franco-German partnership, I question the idea of a duopoly. European construction is based on a well-balanced and respectful partnership between France and Germany."', '"Believe,Construction,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"The partnerships between Schmidt and Giscard, Kohl and Mitterrand, and even between Chirac and Schroeder, have proved that political differences do not mean that we cannot work together."', '"Work,Together,Political"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"We need intelligence services to fight against terrorism, but they have to respect the principles of good relationships between allies and protect personal, confidential data."', '"Respect,Good,Intelligence"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'The first time that I went to the United States was in 1974. I was 20 years old. America was in crisis.', '"Time,America,First Time"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', 'Our only goal is to strengthen the opposition and to avoid the dilemma whereby we only have the choice between Bashar Assad and al-Qaeda.', '"Choice,Avoid,Opposition"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"In August 2012, the international community should have been far more determined in dealing with the Bashar Assad regime."', '"Community,More,Far"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"I must demonstrate I\'m closer to people - a simpler, calmer presence, yet someone who can also make decisions and obtain promised results."', '"People,Someone,Presence"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"People are tired of constant movement, improvisation, and wild scrambling when plans fail."', '"Tired,People,Wild"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"Private life is always, at certain times, a challenge."', '"Life,Private Life,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf3', '"In my own situation, I cannot show anything... And I believe that everybody now understands that, president or not president, one is entitled to have a private life. But of course when one is president, this creates duties and obligations."', '"Life,Believe,Private Life"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf4', '"It\'s never nice to lose someone close to you; unfortunately, life goes on, and we have to make peace with it and move on."', '"Life,Peace,Lose"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf4', 'You never know what battles people fight.', '"Fight,Battles,People"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf4', 'I think rugby is 80 per cent mental.', '"Rugby,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf4', '"As soon as you have an average game, everyone is quick to criticise and say, \'You suck; you shouldn\'t be playing rugby.\'"', '"Game,Everyone,Rugby"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf5', 'One of the deepest functions of a living organisms is to look ahead... to produce future.', '"Future,Look,Living"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf5', 'I had turned my anxiety into my profession.', '"Anxiety,Profession,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf5', 'Evolution is a tinkerer.', 'Evolution', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf5', '"For me, this world of questions and the provisional, this chase after an answer that was always put off to the next day, all that was euphoric. I lived in the future."', '"Future,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf6', '"Very different from eros is philia, a serene love much more akin to friendship, with its reciprocal kindnesses. You love each other for the happy experiences and pleasures you share."', '"Friendship,Love,Happy"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf6', 'Eros is not tranquil - it gives us spikes of happiness rather than a constant feeling of wellbeing. It\'s the love we feel at the beginning of a love affair and corresponds to the expression \'falling in love\' since it is as involuntary an impulse as a physical fall.', '"Love,Happiness,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf6', '"I didn\'t intend \'Hector\' to be a self-help book when I first started writing. I wrote it as a little tale about a psychiatrist, like me, who sets off around the world in order to discover the vital ingredients for happiness."', '"Happiness,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf6', '"Finding love is a fixation now, and that\'s because although romantic love can sometimes cause a lot of suffering, it can also give people peaks of happiness that come very close to our ideal of \'the happy state.\'"', '"Love,Happiness,Romantic"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', 'To love someone is to see a miracle invisible to others.', '"Love,See,Invisible"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', '"Tell me what you read and I\'ll tell you who you are is true enough, but I\'d know you better if you told me what you reread."', '"Me,Better,True"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', 'I love Germany so dearly that I hope there will always be two of them.', '"Love,Hope,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', 'Human love is often but the encounter of two weaknesses.', '"Love,Love Is,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', '"Where does discipline end? Where does cruelty begin? Somewhere between these, thousands of children inhabit a voiceless hell."', '"Discipline,Hell,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf7', 'Men resemble great deserted palaces: the owner occupies only a few rooms and has closed-off wings where he never ventures.', '"Men,Great,Wings"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf8', 'A man loses contact with reality if he is not surrounded by his books.', '"Reality,Man,Surrounded"', '2023-05-29 11:58:00', '2023-05-29 11:58:00'),
	('396640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf8', 'France is delighted at this new opportunity to show the world that when one has the will one can succeed in joining peoples who have been brought close by history.', '"History,Opportunity,World"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"It\'s very refreshing to go away and take a break, to clear your head, and just get into something else."', '"Refreshing,Go,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Makeup is about balance. When the eye makes a statement, the lips should be quiet."', '"Balance,Lips,Makeup"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"True icons are larger than life, unforgettable with an elegance that\'s mesmerizingly timeless."', '"Life,True,Elegance"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"We are not afraid to be a bit different, to make shades that are bold."', '"Bold,Afraid,Shades"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"You create the color first, and then the name that fits. It depends - there are no rules. You watch a fabulous old movie, and you suddenly get inspired by it to create a lipstick shade, or you walk through a gorgeous garden and find the most beautiful flower shade for an eye shadow, and then you name it."', '"Most Beautiful,Beautiful,Flower"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I like beauty to be a bit edgy, not typical. For me, the only rule is looking good."', '"Beauty,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I think there was a freedom in the 1920s and 1930s: a certain liberty and evolution of women.', '"Freedom,Women,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"My mother never wore much make-up, and she was a kind of natural beauty; she knew just how to enhance what she had."', '"Beauty,Natural Beauty,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"My mother and my two grandmothers, I was lucky to have three women around me growing up that were very special, very elegant women, very beautiful women. They were my first step into the beauty world, let\'s say, and then the fashion world, of course."', '"Beauty,Women,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"My interpretation of the word \'ugly\'... I like ugly beauty. That can happen. In France, we have phrase \'jolie laide.\' We like certain women who are not pretty or cute - it\'s the opposite in France of pretty. It\'s more strange and interesting."', '"Beauty,Women,Cute"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Women are very unpredictable.', '"Women,Unpredictable,Women Are"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Women have to find their own personality, their own style, and what suits them the best."', '"Best,Women,Personality"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'My mother hated foundation; she hated having a mask on her face - and she pushed me to build my own vision and concept of beauty for women.', '"Beauty,Women,Vision"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I think everyone deserves to look better and to look good.', '"Good,Look,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I\'m very nostalgic - and I don\'t care.', '"Care,dont Care,Nostalgic"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'A fresh face with a red lip is timeless. It\'s supermodern and relaxed but very chic.', '"Face,Red,Fresh"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I\'ve always loved the way movie stars in the Forties looked when they were off set. Shot poolside or at their home, they always wore a matte red lipstick with practically no foundation - it was how they wore makeup in real life."', '"Life,Home,Stars"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I have always been attracted to faces that are different.', '"Always,Different,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I\'m always looking to the lightweight superproduct that you apply and almost don\'t see. That\'s the ultimate, at least for me."', '"Me,Looking,See"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Makeup can make a woman look more beautiful at every age.', '"Age,Beautiful,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Some people put a lot of fuss around them. I\'m not an entertainer. Let\'s not get things confused.', '"People,Confused,Some People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"From the start, I used a different kind of girl in Nars campaign images. My choice to use models of colour such as Alek Wek, Naomi Campbell and Karen Park Goude was absolutely a deliberate one. I felt that makeup was universal and should apply to everybody."', '"Start,Choice,Girl"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I never stop thinking about names of products. It\'s a process that happens 24 hours a day.', '"Thinking,Day,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I\'ll keep creating modern, deep, rich and adventurous colors and products that inspire creative expression every day."', '"Colors,Day,Rich"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"In a lot of cases, makeup is a fantastic help, and that\'s why women love makeup in general. It\'s a fantastic way to help somebody look great. It\'s not the only way, of course, but it\'s a major accessory, along with hair, clothes, lighting, all those things."', '"Love,Women,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I didn\'t want to create a makeup line for one ethnic group; it had to be multi-ethnic. To me, beauty is beauty. It doesn\'t matter to me what colour the skin is."', '"Beauty,Me,Skin"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"In this world, you do your job, a good job, and that\'s what counts."', '"Good,World,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I think Edie Sedgwick comes back, too. Every five or six years, there is always something about Edie, because she was so modern and stylish and elegant and hippie-ish, all at the same time. So I think that people will always love her."', '"Love,Time,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I met Iman and Jerry Hall and all those girls in the late Seventies right when I started working at the fashion shows in Paris as an assistant.', '"Late,Fashion,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I wanted to be a make up artist. I did it, and the road that I took was quite good."', '"Good,Road,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'It\'s not that I\'m easily shocked. It takes a lot to shock me. And wildness I like. But vulgarity shocks me.', '"Me,Shock,Shocked"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Makeup is very important for a show. It\'s really an accessory on the runway. You have to be sure that it fits the clothes.', '"Important,Clothes,Makeup"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'A woman who hides behind a mask of makeup is still going to have to take it off at some point... and deal with reality.', '"Reality,Woman,Mask"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Wearing colourful eyeliner in a graphic shape is the epitome of make-up as an accessory.', '"Shape,Epitome,Wearing"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I love the architecture magazines and all of the French magazines for decoration or whatever. I end up enjoying them more sometimes than the fashion magazines.', '"Love,Architecture,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I loved working with Avedon.', '"Loved,Working"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I like shocking, but I don\'t like to shock as an automatic process. Sometimes it happens, but it\'s not my main drive."', '"Drive,Process,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Sometimes people are very not sure of themselves, so you really have to give them that confidence. Even models - they need to warm up sometimes on photo shoots."', '"Confidence,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I was a very lucky child because at the age of 16, 17 years old, my parents would buy me clothes from Yves Saint Laurent, which was an incredible luxury at the time, but I was attracted to that whole world. I had a pretty nice little wardrobe by the age of 17."', '"Time,Age,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I really wanted to have a different approach of beauty because when I came to America, they were still heavily, heavily plastic. The ads were so heavily retouched."', '"Beauty,America,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'My goal was always to make the girl look real and look beautiful. It didn\'t matter how much makeup. Sometimes it was none at all.', '"Beautiful,Look,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I think it\'s important that you know every detail when you open a store, that you pay attention to everything."', '"Important,Know,Attention"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I always had a vision about beauty in general, so probably that\'s what really drove me into that direction of creating a makeup brand."', '"Beauty,Vision,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Was I a businessman to start with? I\'m not sure. I mean, that comes slowly, when you start having the products out. But at the same time, I was very determined. I knew that I had to make it work. I had no choice."', '"Work,Time,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I\'m always scared of trends. The runways are always so trend-oriented, but I always feel for the women. The real women that buy cosmetics want to see the trends, but they don\'t necessarily go for them. And I always encourage women to find what looks best on them."', '"Best,Women,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I think if you take good care of your skin, you can achieve better make-up."', '"Good,Skin,Care"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Even with - the best make-up in the world won\'t look good if you don\'t cleanse and exfoliate and have a good basic regime. This is why one of my goals has always been to create a skincare line.', '"Best,Good,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"As a make-up artist, you always want to be in a good light, whether you\'re walking down the street or in a restaurant. It is a very key element to me; you can\'t apply good make-up in a bad light."', '"Good,Restaurant,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I think less is more when it comes to make-up; this really helps achieve a lighter complexion. Heavy make-up creates a canvas and can dull the skin.', '"Skin,Canvas,Achieve"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I fell in love with New York. I moved here 25 years ago in 1984 after I lived in Paris for six years. In the 1980s, it was the place to be. Here I was able to create NARS, which I would not have been able to create if I stayed in France."', '"Love,New,Place"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'You are born with this love; fashion and beauty are a part of who I am.', '"Beauty,Love,I Am"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I would find myself in these photo shoots with models and makeup, and I got swept up in it all."', '"Myself,Find,Makeup"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"In America, when I first came here, they were used to wearing more make-up - thicker foundation, more Max Factor, that sort of thing. But you have to know who you are and what you look like: if you know yourself a little bit, you don\'t need to follow trends."', '"Look,Yourself,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"It really has stayed practically the same. It wasn\'t like I used to do wild punk make-up: no, I always had the same vision."', '"Vision,Wild,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I\'m not an easily depressed person.', '"Person,Depressed,Easily"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"There was a time when you would dream about, say, movie stars. Now, you virtually follow them into their bathroom when they\'re going to the loo."', '"Time,Stars,Bathroom"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I never thought make-up was like brain surgery.', '"Brain,Never,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"When I was a kid, I loved photography, and I loved makeup."', '"Makeup,Loved,Photography"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I chose makeup over photography because there was something very sensual about makeup that I loved. But photography was always in the back of my mind. That was always something that I was very connected with: looking at magazines, enjoying photography, and then taking pictures myself when I was a kid."', '"Myself,Mind,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"When you photograph someone, you have to make them feel good, and you know that they want to look good. It\'s the same relationship that you have when you apply makeup on somebody. We\'re almost like shrinks."', '"Relationship,Good,Feel Good"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I had no connections, and the fashion world was a closed elite. So my mother made appointments for herself with three top Parisian makeup artists and spoke highly about me... she was my first publicist!"', '"Me,World,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"It\'s more fun to have a name rather than a number. I think this gives our products a personality. I get the names from literature, movies, opera, traveling, nature, poetry, sometimes even the street. I keep a small book that I write in. I wake up in the middle of the night and jot down a name for a lipstick or an eyeshadow."', '"Nature,Poetry,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'We love those under-eye circles. It\'s real life.', '"Life,Love,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I love the dramatic idea of having nothing on.', '"Love,Nothing,Dramatic"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I love strong looks, so to me, no makeup is strong. As long as it makes a statement, that\'s what I like. The girls look very real, and I\'m probably the only makeup artist who will say that I love a woman without makeup."', '"Love,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I remember this time I worked with Linda Evangelista on a shoot for Richard Avedon. I just put grease on her face, and it was beautiful."', '"Time,Beautiful,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I\'ve seen makeup destroy people and make them look bad if it\'s badly done.', '"Look,Bad,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I thought make-up was a very sensual thing.', '"Sensual,Thought,Very"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Being a studio make-up artist and working on magazines was the only thing I wanted to do.', '"Artist,Only,Studio"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"There is a tendency to feature more actresses on covers, but I\'m a big model lover. I grew up watching these models, and they gave me the wish, the need, to work in the fashion industry. I loved watching them - their beauty, the way they worked in front of the camera and that power of transformation, especially in the Seventies."', '"Beauty,Work,Power"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Sometimes I\'m attracted to more odd girls with stronger faces and features or a softer beauty with a lot of character.', '"Beauty,Character,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"It was the early Seventies, and I discovered makeup by going through my mother\'s fashion magazines. I fell in love with the photos, the models, the fashion."', '"Love,Fashion,Mother"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'My vision was to create makeup that was more transparent but with formulas that last. I follow my instincts - it\'s all very spontaneous!', '"Vision,Create,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I don\'t think there\'s a major change between runway and real life anymore.', '"Life,Change,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Women don\'t want to feel like they\'re wearing makeup. I hope I was partly responsible for that.', '"Hope,Women,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'It\'s one thing to read about how makeup is applied. It\'s another thing altogether to watch it being put on.', '"Makeup,One Thing,Watch"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Find your own way, have an open spirit, and believe in your own beauty."', '"Beauty,Believe,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Looking at flowers, simple things in life. I don\'t need to look at gold and a castle; sometimes its very simple things that are very beautiful. I am keeping my eyes fresh to find beauty in many places, and in gold, too, sometimes!"', '"Life,Beauty,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I love so much the models from the \'60s and the \'70s. They were extremely professional, great models who knew how to work the camera so well and loved fashion and had a great sense of style."', '"Love,Work,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I photographed Alek Wek. She was amazing, and nobody knew about her then. It was a really strong photograph of her."', '"Amazing,Nobody,She"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I\'m not so interested in perfect, plastic beauty, and I think it translates in the girls I\'ve shot over the years for Nars, from Guinevere to Iris to Mariacarla. I love those girls. I love the more interesting faces, with maybe a strange nose, not just the Texan blonde. By picking those girls, I think it\'s changed what I\'ve seen in other campaigns."', '"Beauty,Love,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Working on fashion shows, you work with the designer and try to read his brain - what was in the creative process, what images did he have in his head?"', '"Work,Brain,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Having worked with so many of the geniuses, I\'d learned so much. It\'s the best sort of photography school, to work with people like Penn or Avedon or Meisel."', '"Work,Best,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Kate Moss makes you dream. She has such a passion for art and the creative process.', '"Art,Passion,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'I was spoiled growing up in the 1970s because magazines were publishing the photographs of Helmut Newton and Guy Bourdin without compromise. You really felt that sense of freedom through their images.', '"Freedom,Compromise,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I love to collaborate with artists, like Guy Bourdin and Steven Klein, who don\'t have any boundaries."', '"Love,Boundaries,Guy"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'The \'80s and \'90s were the greatest time to be a makeup artist.', '"Time,Makeup,Artist"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'It\'s very hard for me to photograph someone when I\'m not attracted by who they are.', '"Me,Someone,Hard"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I can\'t remember the first time, but I\'ve worked with supermodels almost from day one."', '"Time,Day,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I made contours and all that, but in real life, you have to be very careful with that because you can go out in the street and look terrible. All those girls who show how to do contour, they do it quite well, but they\'re like makeup artists. They\'re in artificial light."', '"Life,Look,Light"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Transparency is more sexy than a full, pancake finish."', '"Sexy,Transparency,Finish"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'It was never in my mind to be famous.', '"Famous,Mind,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"People have to learn that everybody is the same. If you wake up in the morning, even if you\'re a movie star, you look like everybody else. The reality is that makeup is there to help. That\'s what it\'s for."', '"Morning,Reality,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I launched NARS with 12 shades of lipsticks, and many, many launches later, I\'m still most proud of our lipsticks."', '"Proud,Shades,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Women are being more experimental with eye color.', '"Women,More,Eye"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"Makeup is an accessory to fashion. You buy a bag, you buy shoes, you put on eyeliner, you buy a lipstick, makeup compliments the clothes."', '"Shoes,Bag,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"You can look glamorous even if you\'re a housewife, any job you have."', '"Look,Glamorous,Job"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', '"I hate knowing where people go to the bathroom. You follow them going to pee, to eat - I hate everything when it comes to reality shows!"', '"Reality,Hate,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'Go with what you\'re attracted to.', '"Go,Attracted,You"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdf9', 'We don\'t tell women how to look but give them the products and inspiration they need to feel and look beautiful.', '"Women,Beautiful,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfa', '"I checked on the Internet this morning, and I realized that with five individual world titles, I was level with my elders Florian Rousseau and Arnaud Tournant, who were the sprint leaders in France when I started at the French Institute of Sports and taught me everything. I had the chance to overtake them, and I did it."', '"Morning,Chance,Sports"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfa', '"It\'s good to break records, I love it."', '"Love,Good,Break"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfa', '"A sprinter is never satisfied; otherwise, he is not a sprinter."', '"Never,Satisfied,He"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfb', 'I have no sense of nostalgia. Tomorrow is what interests me.', '"Tomorrow,Me,No Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfb', '"The passion for art is, as for believers, very religious. It unites people, its message is of common humanity. Art has become my religion - others pray in church. It\'s a banality, but you don\'t possess art, it possesses you. It\'s like falling in love."', '"Love,Art,Religion"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfb', '"My mission is not to forbid French art. If the quality is there, I buy; if the quality isn\'t there, I don\'t."', '"Art,Quality,Mission"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfb', '"The Italians live well. They have problems, like all countries, but they are well-dressed, the women are pretty."', '"Women,Problems,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"Gestures, in love, are incomparably more attractive, effective and valuable than words."', '"Love,Words,Attractive"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Everything comes in time to those who can wait.', '"Time,Wait,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'It is my feeling that Time ripens all things; with Time all things are revealed; Time is the father of truth.', '"Truth,Time,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Tell the truth and shame the devil.', '"Truth,Devil,Shame"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Science without conscience is the death of the soul.', '"Science,Death,Soul"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Ignorance is the mother of all evils.', '"Ignorance,Mother,Evils"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"We always long for the forbidden things, and desire what is denied us."', '"Long,Always,Desire"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"When I drink, I think; and when I think, I drink."', '"Drink,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"From the gut comes the strut, and where hunger reigns, strength abstains."', '"Strength,Hunger,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'A habit does not a monk make.', '"Habit,Monk,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'To good and true love fear is forever affixed.', '"Love,Good,Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"If the skies fall, one may hope to catch larks."', '"Hope,Fall,Catch"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Half the world does not know how the other half lives.', '"World,Know,Half"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Debts and lies are generally mixed together.', '"Together,Lies,Mixed"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"I place no hope in my strength, nor in my works: but all my confidence is in God my protector, who never abandons those who have put all their hope and thought in him."', '"God,Hope,Strength"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"I have known many who could not when they would, for they had not done it when they could."', '"Done,Who,Would"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'There are more old drunkards than old physicians.', '"Old,More,Than"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'The farce is finished. I go to seek a vast perhaps.', '"Go,Finished,Seek"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'If you wish to avoid seeing a fool you must first break your looking glass.', '"Fool,Looking,Glass"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"The right moment wears a full head of hair: when it has been missed, you can\'t get it back; it\'s bald in the back of the head and never turns around."', '"Moment,Hair,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'I won\'t undertake war until I have tried all the arts and means of peace.', '"War,Peace,Tried"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Misery is the company of lawsuits.', '"Legal,Company,Misery"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Remove idleness from the world and soon the arts of Cupid would perish.', '"World,Soon,Idleness"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"The scent of wine, oh how much more agreeable, laughing, praying, celestial and delicious it is than that of oil!"', '"Scent,Wine,More"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"The remedy for thirst? It is the opposite of the one for a dog bite: run always after a dog, he\'ll never bite you; drink always before thirst, and it will never overtake you."', '"Will,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Nature abhors a vacuum.', '"Nature,Vacuum,Abhors"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"Time, which wears down and diminishes all things, augments and increases good deeds, because a good turn liberally offered to a reasonable man grows continually through noble thought and memory."', '"Time,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"For he who can wait, everything comes in time."', '"Time,Wait,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'No clock is more regular than the belly.', '"Clock,More,Belly"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"How shall I be able to rule over others, that have not full power and command of myself?"', '"Power,Myself,Others"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'One falls to the ground in trying to sit on two stools.', '"Trying,Ground,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'I drink no more than a sponge.', '"Drink,More,Sponge"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"Believe me, \'tis a godlike thing to lend; to owe is a heroic virtue."', '"Me,Believe,Owe"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'In their rules there was only one clause: Do what you will.', '"Rules,Will,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"It is better to write of laughter than of tears, for laughter is the property of man."', '"Laughter,Man,Tears"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"There is no truer cause of unhappiness amongst men than, where naturally expecting charity and benevolence, they receive harm and vexation."', '"Men,Charity,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"Friends, you will notice that in this world there are many more ballocks than men. Remember this."', '"Men,World,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'Frugality is for the vulgar.', '"Vulgar,Frugality"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"How can I govern others, who can\'t even govern myself?"', '"Myself,Others,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"Because just as arms have no force outside if there is no counsel within a house, study is vain and counsel useless that is not put to virtuous effect when the time calls."', '"Time,Useless,House"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', '"When undertaking marriage, everyone must be the judge of his own thoughts, and take counsel from himself."', '"Marriage,Thoughts,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfc', 'How do you know antiquity was foolish? How do you know the present is wise? Who made it foolish? Who made it wise?', '"Wise,Know,Present"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'I have always preferred the reflection of the life to life itself.', '"Life,Reflection,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'Is the cinema more important than life?', '"Life,Cinema,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'Film lovers are sick people.', '"Movies,People,Sick"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"The film of tomorrow will not be directed by civil servants of the camera, but by artists for whom shooting a film constitutes a wonderful and thrilling adventure."', '"Tomorrow,Will,Camera"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"In love, women are professionals, men are amateurs."', '"Love,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"When humor can be made to alternate with melancholy, one has a success, but when the same things are funny and melancholic at the same time, it\'s just wonderful."', '"Funny,Success,Time"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I want my audience to be constantly captivated, bewitched, so that it leaves the theatre dazed, stunned to be back on the pavement."', '"Back,Theatre,Audience"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'Taste is a result of a thousand distastes.', '"Result,Taste,Thousand"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"To be a film-maker, you are almost forced to be surrounded by contradictions... You must have talents of so many different kinds - talents that are contradictory."', '"Surrounded,Must,Almost"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"During the war, I saw many films that made me fall in love with the cinema."', '"Love,War,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"An actor is never so great as when he reminds you of an animal - falling like a cat, lying like a dog, moving like a fox."', '"Great,Animal,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"The film of tomorrow will resemble the person who made it, and the number of spectators will be proportional to the number of friends the director has."', '"Tomorrow,Will,Person"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"Hitchcock loves to be misunderstood, because he has based his whole life around misunderstandings."', '"Life,Misunderstood,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'The film of tomorrow will be an act of love.', '"Love,Tomorrow,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I\'ve always had the impression that real militants are like cleaning women, doing a thankless, daily but necessary job."', '"Women,Daily,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"The film of tomorrow appears to me as even more personal than an individual and autobiographical novel, like a confession, or a diary."', '"Tomorrow,Me,Diary"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'Some day I\'ll make a film that critics will like. When I have money to waste.', '"Money,Day,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"At first, I wasn\'t sure whether I\'d be a critic or a filmmaker, but I knew it would be something like that."', '"First,Something,Like"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I had thought of writing, actually, and that later on I\'d be a novelist."', '"Writing,Thought,Had"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I\'d skip school regularly to see movies - even in the morning, in the small Parisian theaters that opened early."', '"Morning,Movies,School"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I prefer to be busy all day long, and when you work for someone else, you\'re not busy enough."', '"Work,Busy,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', 'What switched me to films was the flood of American pictures into Paris after the Liberation.', '"Me,American,Liberation"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"If I have some free time, I leave Paris with some books about the cinema. If I\'m not filming, I\'m watching films."', '"Time,Cinema,Free"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I may find myself changing my notions about what I want to do right in the middle of a film. And on days when I\'m feeling merry, I shoot merry scenes, and on gloomy days, I shoot gloomy ones."', '"Myself,Find,Shoot"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdfe', '"I am less instinctive as I try to be more professional - about the music, about the sound."', '"Music,I Am,Professional"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdff', 'But where are the snows of yester year?', '"Year,Where"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdff', 'Good talkers are only found in Paris.', '"Good,Only,Found"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fdff', 'My days are gone a-wandering.', '"Gone,Days"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', 'Sustainable development is a fundamental break that\'s going to reshuffle the entire deck. There are companies today that are going to dominate in the future simply because they understand that.', '"Future,Today,Sustainable Development"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"You don\'t buy luxury to enter a community, but to set yourself apart from others."', '"Community,Yourself,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', 'I closely follow everything about user interface or human-computer interface: technology that makes computers closer to the way the human being actually functions.', '"Technology,Computers,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"I like to discover new things, and I\'m always testing new apps."', '"New,Always,New Things"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"There\'s a strength to being able to look at products through a customer\'s eyes, but it is also dangerous."', '"Strength,Eyes,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', 'The first PC that I actually bought myself was a Toshiba Papman in 1985. This model was one of the very first laptops; I remember that it was a revolution at the time!', '"Time,Myself,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"I started buying on the Internet quite rapidly, as early as 1995."', '"Internet,Early,Buying"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"I have a regular, normal private life."', '"Life,Private Life,Normal"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"In a recession, you must be able to call into question everything you\'ve done before."', '"Done,Everything,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"I\'d never buy something, even if it\'s a great brand, that is a competitor to something I already own; that\'s insane."', '"Great,Never,Own"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', '"Linguistics is a good way of defining the culture of a brand. The vocabulary used by sports and lifestyle brands - running, fitness, training, motorsports - is all about functionality, whereas the vocabulary of the luxury business - handbags, ready-to-wear - is all about the product."', '"Business,Good,Fitness"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe03', 'Luxury hasn\'t been democratised; it\'s been globalised.', '"Luxury,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"For me, style is essentially doing things well. If you want to be outrageous, be outrageous with style. If you want to be restrained, be restrained with style. One can\'t specifically define style. It\'s like the perfume to a flower. It\'s a quality you can\'t analyze."', '"Flower,Me,Quality"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"I\'m not going to talk about Picasso. I have done my duty to those memories. I have had a great career as an artist myself, you know. I\'m not here just because I\'ve spent time with Picasso."', '"Time,Great,Memories"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"Matisse was my God. I\'m a French artist, that\'s for sure. I am color-oriented and what you might call a composer. I am not pouring my guts out; I keep them inside."', '"God,I Am,Inside"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"What I like about the American woman is she usually has a lot of dynamism. In the U.S., women have a tendency to go forward, to be more exaggerated than in Europe. Many times the rough ideas come from the States, then they are refined in Europe. The American women and the French women are still the best-dressed."', '"Women,Woman,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"I really think that if I had met Picasso during peacetime, nothing would have happened."', '"Nothing,Happened,Think"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', 'To change your mind about something is always difficult. I think that people who are big enough to admit they were wrong can be counted on your fingers.', '"Change,Mind,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"I don\'t write diaries and things like that, but I have a fantastic memory. I call that like a magic carpet. I can really concentrate and travel back in the past I don\'t know how many years from now and evoke that space if I wanted."', '"Space,Travel,Past"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe04', '"\'Matisse and Picasso\' is a little like Plato after Socrates. Socrates only taught in words. He didn\'t write. And after that, you had Plato and Aristotle to write about what he had said. I write about them because they didn\'t write about them."', '"Words,Because,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe05', 'I never get bored. There isn\'t enough time in the day for me.', '"Time,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe05', '"When I write, it is always the melody that comes first, and it just happens to be the case that the most beautiful tunes are sad, and the lyrics follow the mood of the melody."', '"Sad,Most Beautiful,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe05', '"In France, the image I had was of a shy girl - a poor lonely girl and not too good-looking. When I went to England, I had another image. I felt the journalists were much more interested in my looks than in my songs."', '"Shy,Poor,Image"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe05', 'I feel happy and secure when I\'m on my bed with a good book... I forget everything which is terrible in our world.', '"Good,World,Feel"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'A dress makes no sense unless it inspires men to take it off of you.', '"Men,Dress,No Sense"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'Art must take reality by surprise.', '"Art,Reality,Surprise"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"To jealousy, nothing is more frightful than laughter."', '"Jealousy,Laughter,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"Of course the illusion of art is to make one believe that great literature is very close to life, but exactly the opposite is true. Life is amorphous, literature is formal."', '"Life,Art,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'The one thing I regret is that I will never have time to read all the books I want to read.', '"Time,Regret,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'Jazz music is an intensified feeling of nonchalance.', '"Music,Jazz,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'I always believe things are going to work out.', '"Work,Hope,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"One can never speak enough of the virtues, the dangers, the power of shared laughter."', '"Power,Humor,Laughter"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"Marriage? It\'s like asparagus eaten with vinaigrette or hollandaise, a matter of taste but of no importance."', '"Marriage,Matter,Taste"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'It would be bad form for me to describe people I don\'t know and don\'t understand.', '"Me,Bad,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"All my life, I will continue obstinately to write about love, solitude and passion among the kind of people I know. The rest don\'t interest me."', '"Life,Love,Passion"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"Writing is a question of finding a certain rhythm. I compare it to the rhythms of jazz. Much of the time life is a sort of rhythmic progression of three characters. If one tells oneself that life is like that, one feels it less arbitrary."', '"Life,Time,Life Is A"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"I dreamt of being a writer once I started to read. I started to write \'Bonjour Tristesse\' in bistros around the Sorbonne. I finished it, I sent it to editors. It was accepted."', '"Once,Finished,Being"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"After Proust, there are certain things that simply cannot be done again. He marks off for you the boundaries of your talent."', '"Talent,Done,Boundaries"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'Every time I see a film about Joan of Arc I\'m convinced she\'ll get away with it. It\'s the only way to get through life.', '"Life,Time,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"You should celebrate the end of a love affair as they celebrate death in New Orleans, with songs, laughter, dancing and a lot of wine."', '"Love,Death,Celebrate"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'I\'ve read Proust and Stendhal. That keeps you in your place.', '"Place,Your,Read"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'I\'ve tried very hard and I\'ve never found any resemblance between the people I know and the people in my novels.', '"People,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'Every little girl knows about love. It is only her capacity to suffer because of it that increases.', '"Love,Girl,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"Much of the time life is a sort of rhythmic progression of three characters. If one tells oneself that life is like that, one feels it less arbitrary."', '"Life,Time,Life Is A"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'For me writing is a question of finding a certain rhythm. I compare it to the rhythms of jazz.', '"Me,Jazz,Compare"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', '"It seems to me that there are two kinds of trickery: the \'fronts\' people assume before one another\'s eyes, and the \'front\' a writer puts on the face of reality."', '"Eyes,Reality,Face"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe06', 'I had a strong desire to write and some free time.', '"Time,Free,Desire"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"If Yugoslavia is to exist, it can exist only as an alliance, a confederation of independent states."', '"Independent,Only,Alliance"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', 'Let\'s make a deal with the Serbs. Neither history nor emotion in the Balkans will permit multinationalism. We have to give up on the illusion of the last eight years... Dayton isn\'t working. Nobody - except diplomats and petty officials - believes in a sovereign Bosnia and the Dayton accords.', '"History,Illusion,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"The Muslims wanted to reign over the whole of Mostar, then gain ground to the sea and finally create an Islamic state. That is what our Croatians defend themselves against."', '"Sea,Create,Ground"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"Then, as if that\'s not enough, then they declare that my wife is Jewish or Serbian. Luckily for me, she never was either, although many wives are. And so on and so forth spreading lies."', '"Wife,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"Whatever happened after the liberation of Krajina, this was in no way a violation of human rights by Croatian authorities."', '"Way,Whatever,Liberation"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"The estimated loss of up to six million dead is founded too much on both emotional, biased testimonies and on exaggerated data in the postwar reckonings of war crimes and on the squaring of accounts with the defeated."', '"War,Dead,Loss"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"I joined the anti-Fascist struggle with my best friend, who was a Jew."', '"Best,Struggle,Friend"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', 'The West wanted to avoid an Islamic state in Europe.', '"Avoid,Europe,State"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"All sorts of other lies are being spread today, I do not know what else they will invent. I\'ve heard that I\'m of Jewish descent, but I found, I knew of my ancestors in Zagorje from around 350 years ago, and I said, maybe it would be good to have some of that, I guess I would be richer, I might not have become a Communist."', '"Good,Today,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', '"I haven\'t mentioned another argument, The Hague tribunal. It is clear our generals and all of you who are sitting here now with me could end up there, too."', '"Me,End,Argument"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe07', 'You should give no indication that we wish the three-way division of Bosnia.', '"Wish,Division,Bosnia"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"If you find a path with no obstacles, it probably doesn\'t lead anywhere."', '"Path,Obstacles,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'The most important thing that parents can teach their children is how to get along without them.', '"Children,Parents,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"Criticism, like rain, should be gentle enough to nourish a man\'s growth without destroying his roots."', '"Rain,Growth,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'We find comfort among those who agree with us - growth among those who don\'t.', '"Growth,Comfort,Find"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"Everyone is trying to accomplish something big, not realizing that life is made up of little things."', '"Life,Little Things,Big"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'A father is a man who expects his son to be as good a man as he meant to be.', '"Good,Dad,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'A baby is born with a need to be loved - and never outgrows it.', '"Parenting,Never,Born"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Most smiles are started by another smile.', '"Smile,Smiles,Started"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'I think the next best thing to solving a problem is finding some humor in it.', '"Best,Humor,Next"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Gossip needn\'t be false to be evil - there\'s a lot of truth that shouldn\'t be passed around.', '"Truth,Evil,Gossip"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"If a fellow isn\'t thankful for what he\'s got, he isn\'t likely to be thankful for what he\'s going to get."', '"Thankful,Thanksgiving,He"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Real generosity is doing something nice for someone who will never find out.', '"Will,Real,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"Many folks think they aren\'t good at earning money, when what they don\'t know is how to use it."', '"Money,Good,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"Why not upset the apple cart? If you don\'t, the apples will rot anyway."', '"Will,Upset,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'There\'s nothing that can help you understand your beliefs more than trying to explain them to an inquisitive child.', '"Nothing,Help,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'We\'ve put more effort into helping folks reach old age than into helping them enjoy it.', '"Age,Effort,Old Age"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'It\'s hard to detect good luck - it looks so much like something you\'ve earned.', '"Good,Luck,Good Luck"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'The reason there\'s so much ignorance is that those who have it are so eager to share it.', '"Ignorance,Reason,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Kindness makes a fellow feel good whether it\'s being done to him or by him.', '"Good,Feel Good,Kindness"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Modern man is frantically trying to earn enough to buy things he\'s too busy to enjoy.', '"Busy,Man,Enough"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"We\'re all generous, but with different things, like time, money, talent - criticism."', '"Money,Time,Talent"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"A man\'s conscience, like a warning line on the highway, tells him what he shouldn\'t do - but it does not keep him from doing it."', '"Man,Doing,Conscience"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"Habit is something you can do without thinking, which is why most of us have so many of them."', '"Thinking,Habit,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'I\'d rather see folks doubt what\'s true than accept what isn\'t.', '"True,Accept,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"The more you learn to live without, the more you\'ll have to live with."', '"Live,More,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'A leading authority is anyone who has guessed right more than once.', '"Right,More,Authority"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', 'Maybe a person\'s time would be as well spent raising food as raising money to buy food.', '"Money,Time,Food"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe08', '"A child, like your stomach, doesn\'t need all you can afford to give it."', '"Stomach,Your,Child"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"A real man loves his wife, and places his family as the most important thing in life. Nothing has brought me more peace and content in life than simply being a good husband and father."', '"Life,Family,Peace"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'There is no technology today that cannot be defeated by social engineering.', '"Technology,Today,Engineering"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"The police can\'t protect consumers. People need to be more aware and educated about identity theft. You need to be a little bit wiser, a little bit smarter and there\'s nothing wrong with being skeptical. We live in a time when if you make it easy for someone to steal from you, someone will."', '"Time,Police,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'There\'s no such thing as a foolproof system. That idea fails to take into account the creativity of fools.', '"Creativity,System,Fools"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Why do the Yankees always win? The other team can\'t stop looking at the pinstripes.', '"Looking,Win,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Technology breeds crime and we are constantly trying to develop technology to stay one step ahead of the person trying to use it negatively.', '"Technology,Step,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"You have to think a little smarter, be proactive, not reactive."', '"Proactive,Think,Little"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I don\'t use a debit card. The safest thing is a credit card because you\'re using the bank\'s money. If someone accesses your information, they are stealing the bank\'s money, not yours."', '"Money,Information,Credit"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Most people are fascinated by what I did as a teenager, but when I look back at my life, I don\'t think very much about those years. I was an opportunist and got away with things because I was very young, but I went to prison and came out and remade my life."', '"Life,Look,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'The law sometimes sleeps; it never dies.', '"Law,Sometimes,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"People say that life is short, but it isn\'t short. It\'s very long."', '"Life,Life Is Short,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"We all grow up. Hopefully, we get wiser. Age brings wisdom, and fatherhood changes one\'s life completely."', '"Life,Wisdom,Age"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If you look at any successful professional - a salesperson, a marketer, a real estate agent, a trader - they all have the same qualities as the con man. The only difference is that one side uses their talents in the right direction and the con man is taking the easy way out."', '"Man,Look,Direction"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'A real man loves and respects his wife and is not only a good father but a man that his kids want to call \'Daddy.\'', '"Good,Wife,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"The Internet is a wonderful thing, but it opens the door to many crimes, so you have to stay ahead of it."', '"Internet,Door,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Airline pilots are men to be admired and respected. Men to be trusted. Men of means. And you don\'t expect an airline pilot to be a local resident. Or a check swindler.', '"Men,Pilot,Check"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Every breach you look at occurred because somebody inside did something they weren\'t supposed to do. Sometimes there\'s an accomplice, but most of the time, it\'s innocent."', '"Time,Look,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Nothing has brought me more love, joy and peace than being a good husband and good daddy."', '"Love,Peace,Good"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"It\'s about taking the time to research and think things out. Honest people and criminals do the same thing; just the direction, good or bad, is different."', '"Time,Good,Research"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"You cannot rely on the police, you cannot rely on the government, you cannot rely on the bank to protect you."', '"Government,Police,Bank"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I was a millionaire twice over and half again before I was twenty-one. I stole every nickel of it and blew the bulk of the bundle on fine threads, gourmet foods, luxurious lodgings, fantastic foxes, fine wheels, and other sensual goodies."', '"Fine,Sensual,Twice"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'The Internet can be used to hurt many people.', '"Internet,People,Hurt"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Mostly, cybercriminals are motivated to commit crime for financial gain."', '"Financial,Gain,Motivated"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I use a shredder for bank statements and phone bills. Most people use ribbon shredders that cut things straight: we can put those back together in an hour. Look for a security microcut shredder, which cuts papers into confetti."', '"Together,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'You can sit in a room and create anything you want on a laptop. That\'s why the real con men are gone.', '"Men,Laptop,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Whether you\'re earning $7 an hour or $700,000 a year, it\'s very important to protect your credit rating."', '"Important,Credit,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If you took a child in London and took their iPhone and took them somewhere else in the country, they\'d probably not be able to find their way back. That\'s a shame."', '"Way,Country,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"It\'s amazing to me that we live in such a wonderful country where anyone can have a problem in life and get up, dust themselves off and start all over again."', '"Life,Amazing,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'You have to believe in what you do. Take something you truly believe in and go about it in an honest way.', '"Believe,Way,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If I had the uniform on, you didn\'t doubt for a moment I was a pilot. No one ever blinked an eye if I tried to cash a cheque wearing that uniform."', '"Moment,Doubt,Uniform"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Christopher Walken and Nathalie Baye played my parents so well that I really thought I was in my living room at Christmas. My mother couldn\'t have been played more correctly.', '"Christmas,Parents,Living Room"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"At the FBI, very rarely do they investigate crime under $100,000."', '"FBI,Very,Investigate"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If I had been brilliant or a genius, I wouldn\'t have needed to break the law just to survive."', '"Law,Genius,Survive"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I wasn\'t a Pan Am pilot or any other kind of pilot.', '"Pilot,Kind,Pan"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I was just a guy who ran away from home at 16 because my parents were getting a divorce and the judge was making me choose which parent to live with. I didn\'t want to make that choice. I ended up in New York City.', '"Home,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'What I did in my youth is hundreds of times easier today. Technology breeds crime.', '"Technology,Today,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Every form of payment has some risk associated with it.', '"Payment,Risk,Some"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I was an opportunist and got away with things because I was very young, but I went to prison and came out and remade my life."', '"Life,My Life,Prison"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Criminals look at identity theft and say only 1 in 700 criminals gets convicted of it. And they look at check forgery and they know that for every 1,400 forgers arrested, only about 123 get convicted and about 26 go to jail. So the rewards are great, but the risks are very slim. So that\'s one of the reasons that make it very popular."', '"Great,Look,Risks"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I\'m a true believer that you have a moral obligation to keep your employees honest, and that is why you have controls, so I\'m never tempted or put in a position where I could do something to defraud my employer."', '"True,Never,Why"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"By the time I had reached the age of 16, in the 10th grade, my parents, after 22 years of marriage, one day decided to get a divorce."', '"Time,Age,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I don\'t do online banking.', '"Banking,Online"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Every case involving cybercrime that I\'ve been involved in, I\'ve never found a master criminal sitting somewhere in Russia or Hong Kong or Beijing. It always ends up that somebody at the company did something they weren\'t supposed to do. They read an email, went to a website they weren\'t supposed to."', '"Website,Company,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"When people ask me about being portrayed onscreen by Leonardo DiCaprio, I always say, \'I love it - no matter how old I get, people are going to think that\'s what I look like.\'"', '"Love,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I would have thought technology would have made it harder to do what I did.', '"Technology,Made,Harder"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I partied in every capital in Europe, basked on all the famous beaches, and good-timed it in South America, the South Seas, the Orient, and the more palatable portions of Africa."', '"Famous,America,Africa"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I use a credit card for everything - and I choose one of the ones which gives you money back.', '"Money,Back,Credit"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I have to be honest with you: When the FBI let me out of prison early to advise the agency on preventing fraud, I wasn\'t a changed person. I wasn\'t rehabilitated. But when I started working with the FBI, one of the most ethical groups of men and women in the world, I couldn\'t help but have some of that character rub off on me."', '"Women,Men,Character"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"The biggest thing that concerns me is when we start getting countries using cybercrime to shut down infrastructure, electricity, communications systems, the Internet, et cetera."', '"Me,Internet,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I don\'t believe that a piece of paper will excuse my actions. In the end, only my actions will."', '"Believe,Will,End"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If I had walked into a dry cleaning store, and I had looked over, and the register drawer was open with money inside, I wouldn\'t have taken it."', '"Money,Cleaning,Open"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If I wanted to lay down a baby con, I could say I was the product of a broken home. But I\'d only be bum-rapping my parents."', '"Home,Parents,Product"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"We buy into the computer, and everything that comes from the computer, we believe to be the truth."', '"Truth,Believe,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Had I been older - maybe 25 or 30 - I would have never tried half the things I did because I would have rationalized everything and never did it.', '"Never,Everything,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Too many of us are vulnerable, and I look forward to working with AARP to advise people about the safest ways to conduct their financial transactions and manage social media."', '"Look,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"In all the years I\'ve taught at the FBI Academy, I\'ve only seen crime get easier, faster, and harder to detect."', '"Seen,Only,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'The front of a cheque alone gives someone enough information to steal your identity.', '"Alone,Information,Identity"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I went from 198 pounds to 109 while I was in prison in France, and I had to tie my clothes on with rope."', '"Prison,Clothes,Rope"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"When people write about me, they usually start off with the headline \'World\'s Greatest Con Man.\'"', '"Man,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I was always accepted at par value. I wore the uniform of a Pan Am pilot; therefore, I must be a Pan Am pilot."', '"Value,Always,Uniform"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Had I been older, I would\'ve never been able to pull it off because I would\'ve analyzed it to death. When I was 16, there was no such thing as \'what if.\'"', '"Death,Never,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If my forgeries looked as bad as the CBS documents, it would have been \'Catch Me In Two Days\'."', '"Me,Bad,Two"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Banks are so protected from liability they would have to really do something that was their mistake in order for them to be liable for it. Banks don\'t look at signatures. They\'re processing millions of checks and they have very little liability.', '"Look,Mistake,Order"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"In the old days, a con man would be good looking, suave, well dressed, well spoken and presented themselves real well. Those days are gone because it\'s not necessary. The people committing these crimes are doing them from hundreds of miles away."', '"Good,Man,Looking"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'My proudest moment was probably when my oldest boy finished law school and went on to become an FBI agent. It was just beyond my imagination that - with my background - my own son would become an FBI agent.', '"Imagination,Moment,Law"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I think my wife understood from the day I met her how important she was to me and how important it was for me becoming a husband and a father.', '"Wife,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If you happen to tell me where you were born, your date of birth and that kind of information, then I\'m 98 percent of the way to stealing your identity."', '"Me,Information,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"When \'Catch Me If You Can\' was published back in 1980, I never dreamed that it would become a bestseller, much less a major motion picture and now a big Broadway musical. What\'s amazing about the book is that it has never gone out of print."', '"Amazing,Me,Picture"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I was very blessed it was Steven Spielberg who made the movie. He was very much into the redemption side of the story. They asked him in an interview why he had owned the rights to this story for 20 years before he made the movie, and he said, \'I wanted to see what the real Frank Abagnale did with his life before I immortalised him on film.\'"', '"Life,Blessed,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'It\'s quite flattering to have Leonardo DiCaprio play you in the movie. He\'s a great-looking young man.', '"Man,Young,Young Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I served my time and came out of prison when I was just 26 and have worked with the government for 37 years. But people only remember me for what I did before that.', '"Time,Government,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I speak at a lot of universities, and people are always worried about Facebook, and when I explain how to use it properly, they immediately go back and make those changes."', '"People,Back,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Criminals know that if they stay under certain thresholds, nobody is going to come after them."', '"Nobody,Know,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'You have to be smarter and a wiser businessperson and consumer. You have to learn to protect yourself through education.', '"Education,Yourself,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I never use debit cards. I only use credit cards. This way, if someone does get my account number... and charges $1 million, by federal law, my liability is zero."', '"Law,Way,Credit"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I taught at the FBI for four decades - how to think outside of the box and deal with social engineering.', '"Engineering,Outside,Four"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If you tell me your name and date of birth, that\'s all I need to steal your identity."', '"Me,Identity,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"While I was on an undercover assignment in Texas, I met my wife, Kelly."', '"Wife,Assignment,Texas"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I owe a debt to my country 800 times greater than I could ever repay.', '"Country,Debt,Owe"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"When I look back at my life now, I\'m not amazed by what I did at 16 to 21."', '"Life,Look,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"As the lawyer, I found most of it was a matter of research, which I was great at - that\'s what I did to death - and then basically persuading people that you\'re right, and they\'re wrong... I found that the easiest of all the professions to impersonate."', '"Death,Great,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"People have found very significant and simple ways to cheat their employer and get money out of their employers, and many companies lack good internal controls."', '"Money,Good,Simple"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I spent five years of my youth in prison - some very bad prisons.', '"Youth,Bad,Prison"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'You have to be very limited in who you give your social security number to.', '"Security,Your,Social"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I contend that there really are no more con men. There\'s no need for con men anymore. There\'s no need for the very sophisticated, suave guy, the well-dressed guy. Today, you steal with the computer from thousands of miles away - from China, from Libya, from Hong Kong. Your victim\'s never going to see you, so there\'s no need to be any of that."', '"Men,Today,See"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"The truth is, your identity already has been stolen."', '"Truth,Identity,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"One of the most popular scams is what they call account takeover. You write me a check, and I simply go online to a check-printing service and order 200 checks with your account information."', '"Me,Service,Information"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Most people don\'t reconcile their bank accounts.', '"People,Bank,Most"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"We should be very concerned: if identity theft is so simple to do, what\'s to stop me from entering this country and assuming the identity of someone else for the sole purpose of living here illegally for terrorist reasons? That alone would be a concern."', '"Alone,Simple,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"We really need to get control over Social Security numbers. My children\'s generation, they\'re past it. But their children should be able to have a number that is secure."', '"Past,Children,Control"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"It\'s really frustrating when you\'re an identity-theft victim, and you go to the police and you say, \'This guy in Florida, he stole my name and got a credit card - this is his address,\' and they say, \'We don\'t have jurisdiction in Florida. You need to go to the FBI.\'"', '"Police,Credit,Name"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"One thing I\'ve found is that if you educate and show people the risk, they will do something about it."', '"People,Will,Something"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"My father was never really the con-man type that the film shows him to be: he was straight as an arrow, though he did have problems with the IRS."', '"Problems,Father,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I\'m so different from the egotistical, self-centred person I was when I did those things. And to watch someone acting out your memories on the screen is like reliving it. Like someone taking you back and showing you what you did."', '"Memories,Back,Acting"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'People care about others in their immediate network.', '"Care,People,Others"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('396999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"We\'re coming down to an extremely unethical society. Very few colleges offer courses in ethics, and very few companies have a code of conduct or code of ethics."', '"Society,Ethics,Down"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I didn\'t like taking money from individuals.', '"Money,Like,Taking"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I think I was so successful, not because I was brilliant, but because I was so young. I had no fear of consequences."', '"Fear,Young,No Fear"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I didn\'t sit outside the bank and plan. I just went in and ad libbed because I was so young. But I was smart enough to know I would absolutely get caught.', '"Smart,Know,Young"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"It\'s amazing how much information we share in social media, then we wonder why people steal our identity."', '"Amazing,Social Media,Information"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"You get to a point in your life where you go, \'I don\'t remember what I did.\'"', '"Life,Remember,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Most people don\'t recognize me, but they know my name. TSA people rarely recognize my name, ironically, and they are the security people."', '"Me,People,Security"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"If I check into a hotel, a lot of times, they know who I am."', '"I Am,Hotel,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I kept a notebook, a surreptitious journal in which I jotted down phrases, technical data, miscellaneous information, names, dates, places, telephone numbers, thoughts, and a collection of other data I thought was necessary or might prove helpful."', '"Thoughts,Information,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I learned early that class is universally admired.', '"Early,Class,Learned"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Almost any fault, sin or crime is considered more leniently if there\'s a touch of class involved."', '"Sin,Touch,Fault"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I went to the library and learned how checks work. I found out that routing numbers are like zip codes: the checks are sent to the bank that correlates to the routing number. If I manipulate those numbers to a bank far away, it would take longer to get back to the bank, which gave me more time to write more bad checks."', '"Work,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"You should know, whether you live in the U.S. or in the U.K., that your identity has already been stolen."', '"Live,Identity,Know"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"You fight technology with technology, so you have to stay one step ahead of the criminal. It\'s very much a chess game - they make a move, you have to make a move."', '"Technology,Fight,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I have never witnessed, nor will I live long enough to witness, a more simplistic crime than me stealing your identity."', '"Me,Long,Live"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'It is amazing the information we give away. We make it easier and easier for criminals.', '"Amazing,Information,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I\'m glad I\'m a draw. People know that, not only am I the guy that did it, I spent 40 years on the other side."', '"People,Know,Side"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I teach ethics at the FBI academy, which is ironic."', '"Ethics,FBI,Teach"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Unlike most divorces, where the children were usually the first to know, my parents were very good about keeping that a secret."', '"Good,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I make my home in Tulsa.', '"Home,Make"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"I know that people are fascinated by what I did as a teenager, but what I did was immoral, illegal, unethical, and something that I am not proud of - nor will I ever be proud of."', '"I Am,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'I always knew I\'d get caught sooner or later. And I knew I would end up going to prison.', '"Prison,End,Always"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"When I was 28 years old, I thought it would be great to have a movie about my life. I was egotistical and self-centered."', '"Life,Great,My Life"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'A lot of people say I was brilliant. I wasn\'t. I was an opportunist: a young entrepreneur who saw things and took advantage.', '"People,Young,Brilliant"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', 'Everything I have today was because of the love of a woman.', '"Love,Today,Woman"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"A lot of times, when I met somebody and took them out on a date, I obviously didn\'t tell them my background, because I didn\'t think I\'d see them but once or twice."', '"See,Tell,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"There are many ways to manipulate chip cards. For example, a number of years ago when American Express issued the first chip card, criminals would take a small hammer with a little device and bang the chip to destroy it without hurting the physical appearance of the card."', '"Appearance,American,Cards"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe09', '"Only one thing makes a man a man. He loves his wife, is faithful to her, and puts his wife and kids as the most important things in life."', '"Life,Wife,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', 'I destroy things every day in the act of working and often recall a picture I had considered finished in order to rework it.', '"Day,Picture,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', '"Ideally, one should have more material than one can possibly cope with."', '"More,Cope,Than"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', 'I\'m hoping to make a new thing for the world that remains in the mind like a new species of living thing.', '"World,Mind,New"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', '"To put down an ideogram of a table so that people will recognize it as a table is not the work of a painter, but to sense it for a moment as a magic carpet with a leg hanging down at each corner is the beginning of a painter\'s imagination."', '"Work,Imagination,Moment"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', '"It seems to me madness to wake up in the morning and do something other than paint, considering that one may not wake up the following morning."', '"Morning,Me,Wake Up"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', 'Real style is not having a program - it\'s how one behaves in a crisis.', '"Style,Real,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0a', '"The unity in any painter\'s work arises from the fact that a person, brought to a desperate situation, will behave in a certain way... style."', '"Work,Style,Unity"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'It is not to be expected that human nature will change in a day.', '"Nature,Change,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"I believe that in the end the abolition of war, the maintenance of world peace, the adjustment of international questions by pacific means will come through the force of public opinion, which controls nations and peoples."', '"War,Peace,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"I know that military alliances and armament have been the reliance for peace for centuries, but they do not produce peace; and when war comes, as it inevitably does under such conditions, these armaments and alliances but intensify and broaden the conflict."', '"War,Peace,Conflict"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"There will always be disputes between nations which, at times, will inflame the public and threaten conflicts, but the main thing is to educate the people of the world to be ever mindful that there are better means of settling such disputes than by war."', '"War,World,Better"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"I share the opinion of those of broader vision, who see in the signs of the time hope of humanity for peace."', '"Hope,Time,Peace"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"The fact that so many of your people are today residents and citizens of the United States, lending their influence to our civic and economic life, which has meant so much to our development."', '"Life,Today,Influence"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'Public opinion shapes our destinies and guides the progress of human affairs.', '"Progress,Opinion,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"These measures may not constitute an absolute guarantee of peace, but, in my opinion, they constitute the greatest preventive measures ever adopted by nations."', '"Peace,Opinion,May"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'I further value this gift as it gave me an opportunity to accept this distinguished honor in a country so devoted to this cause and whose history marks a wonderful chapter in world development.', '"History,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"I know of no greater work for humanity than in the cause of peace, which can only be achieved by the earnest efforts of nations and peoples."', '"Work,Peace,Humanity"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"There is no short and easy road, no magic cure for those ills which have afflicted mankind from the dawn of history."', '"History,Road,Magic"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"Each one of these treaties is a step for the maintenance of peace, an additional guarantee against war. It is through such machinery that the disputes between nations will be settled and war prevented."', '"War,Peace,Step"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"Have we so soon forgotten those four years of terrible carnage, the greatest war of all time; forgotten the millions of men who gave their lives, who made the supreme sacrifice and who today, beneath the soil of France and Belgium, sleep the eternal sleep?"', '"War,Time,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"If we will maintain our hope and confidence in the genius of our people, they will work out this problem, and their ability and industry will bring us back to normal conditions."', '"Work,Hope,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"To be sure, in some instances these proceedings have been unconstitutional, but we must remember that it is not the first time since a war that there have been changes in governments by such methods."', '"War,Time,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"There has not been a war in South America for fifty years, and I have every confidence that the countries of Central and South America are deeply in earnest in the maintenance of peace."', '"War,Peace,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'It is by such means as the prize offered by your Committee that the attention of the world will be focused and that men and women will be inspired to greater efforts in the interest of peace.', '"Women,Peace,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"Competition in armament, both land and naval, is not only a terrible burden upon the people, but I believe it to be one of the greatest menaces to the peace of the world."', '"Peace,Believe,World"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"It is idle to say that nations can struggle to outdo each other in building armaments and never use them. History demonstrates the contrary, and we have but to go back to the last war to see the appalling effect of nations competing in great armaments."', '"War,History,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'Adequate defense has been the catchword of every militarist for centuries.', '"Defense,Every,Been"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"It is true not all has been accomplished that the earnest advocates would desire, but a start has been made."', '"True,Start,Desire"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"France and Italy have not yet signed this treaty or agreed to naval limitation as between those nations, but I have confidence that in time they will do so."', '"Time,Confidence,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'I do not hesitate to say that the limitation on naval craft between the great naval powers was too high.', '"Great,Craft,High"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"I know of no more important subject to the peace of Europe and the world than the reasonable reduction of armaments, especially in Europe, and of naval armaments throughout the world."', '"Peace,World,Important"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"There are but few naval powers, but there are many land powers."', '"Land,Few,Many"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', '"Certain it is that a great responsibility rests upon the statesmen of all nations, not only to fulfill the promises for reduction in armaments, but to maintain the confidence of the people of the world in the hope of an enduring peace."', '"Hope,Peace,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0b', 'I have often heard it said that the United States is isolated and is not interested in European affairs. I assure you that this is not the case.', '"Not Interested,Said,Interested"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I\'ve got a small, loyal audience, which is great. And I appreciate that. They\'re there for me every time."', '"Time,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I\'m an untrained musician. Untrained musicians don\'t really have any music theory, they don\'t have a lot of rules. We break the rules, but it\'s mostly because we don\'t know what the rules are. It\'s easy for us to go to certain places, so I\'m not surprised that a lot of people were amused by my songwriting style."', '"Music,Style,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"It more or less has the shape of a love song, but \'Crescent Moon\' reflects more my longing for an ancient romantic context that includes wild animals, fire, danger of death, stellar navigation, and seasonal intuition."', '"Love,Death,Romantic"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I like visual images and there are certainly other bands that have strong visual images going all the way back to Elvis Presley, but it\'s kind of like that\'s never really been my bag. Probably because I\'m too shy."', '"Bag,Way,Shy"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"It\'s obvious you shouldn\'t steal, kill or be cruel."', '"Cruel,Obvious,Steal"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I have had UFO experiences, and yet, at the same time, I can easily be convinced that none of it is true. It\'s hard to say whether or not you\'re a believer. I\'ve been interested in that subject matter, like lots of people. Perhaps foolishly, I\'ve allowed some of that stuff to creep into my music."', '"Time,Music,True"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I\'m always looking to rock out. But it isn\'t really about rocking out versus being mellow, in terms of your personal satisfaction. In the end, you just want to be good. When you look at something that\'s really good, it might be Iggy Pop or it might be Leonard Cohen. Whatever it is, you want it to be really good."', '"Good,Look,Satisfaction"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I drive a lot. Just for pleasure. Sometimes I\'ll get in the Cadillac and drive around the city or the country, kind of trying to get lost basically. Y\'know, just see where roads lead."', '"Drive,City,Lost"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"You should never rely on interviews with musicians as being factual. Most of them are mangled and even have made up stuff in them, that is to say, made up stuff by the writer or editor."', '"Never,Up,Say"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', 'For some artists the live performance is the chicken before the egg of writing or recording of repertoire. For other artists the writing or recording of repertoire is the chicken before the egg of live performance.', '"Chicken,Live,Egg"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', 'I\'ve made my records and I\'ve done all the interviews. I\'ve done lots of long tours. I\'ve made stupid videos. I\'ve done all that stuff and learned all the lingo and gone to radio stations and shmoozed with DJs on the air and met retail people.', '"Stupid,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"Some have called we rock and roll performers who never retire \'troubadours.\' I enjoy this misnomer immensely. While there are many differences between me and my distant predecessors in L\'Occitane, I do believe there is a lineage that connects us of the last 70 years with those romantic singers of the High Middle Ages."', '"Romantic,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"The dumber half of the audience - whether they\'re male or female, and a lot of them are male - for some reason responds very quickly to the feminine voice. How can I put it? They kind of instantly react to the female voice in a positive way quicker than they would the male voice."', '"Positive,Way,Voice"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"People go back to the stuff that doesn\'t cost a lot of money and the stuff that you don\'t have to hand money to over and over again. Stuff that you get for free, stuff that your older brother gives you, stuff that you can get out of the local library."', '"Money,Free,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"Bob Dylan is quite a songwriter, and a great singer and musician. I won\'t bother with comparing myself to him, but I will say that I heard his records at a very young age and I still listen to all his records."', '"Age,Great,Myself"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', 'But the truth is that critics are by definition critical. That\'s their job.', '"Truth,Job,Critics"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', 'There\'s more to life than listening to rock music.', '"Life,Music,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I\'m not saying that people have to listen to rock music. It\'s a great, cool thing and it can really be liberating for a lot of people but, hey, so can Charles Dickens so I\'m not going to judge."', '"Cool,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I don\'t make records that way, where I\'m trying to please the marketplace or anything. Not because I have anything against that, it\'s just never been a part of my aesthetic, even when I was with the Pixies."', '"Way,Aesthetic,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"My most cryptic, strange songs might be my most personal, but that isn\'t how people are going to receive them, because they don\'t know the code."', '"People,Know,Strange"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"They\'re a different generation, those kids; kids that are under the age of twelve. They\'re not that impressed by rock music, you know what I mean? They\'re like, it\'s cool and everything, but whatever. They\'re just as impressed by YouTube."', '"Cool,Age,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I certainly have gotten caught up in the music business at various times in my life, mostly because you want to get along with whatever record company you\'re dealing with. I don\'t want to be flaky. I don\'t want to be some temperamental, hard-to-work-with musician."', '"Life,Business,Music"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"If you\'re going to exude naivete, you can\'t really... walk out there like it\'s a Sting show. You can\'t be that well put together and then have this kind of innocent bravado."', '"Walk,Together,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I listen to Neil Young and jazz and classical stations and, if my girlfriend\'s driving, it tends to be Hall & Oates."', '"Jazz,Young,Driving"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"They\'re pretty good actually, Hall & Oates. I gotta give them credit. They got a lot of toe-tappers."', '"Good,Credit,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"The first thing that inspires any song is a chord progression. When I have one I really like, I get into the lyrics even more."', '"Song,More,First"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', 'I have two step-kids and one of my own on the way. That\'s three college funds.', '"Way,Three,My Own"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I don\'t want to do children\'s music. I write kids songs, but the kids songs I write are for my kids - like when I\'m putting them to bed. We sing some song that we made up but I don\'t want to make a record like that."', '"Music,Song,Children"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"It\'s sour grapes, I admit, I want to be more famous so people are examining my work couplet by couplet, you know what I mean? That\'s the level where I want to go."', '"Work,Famous,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I think everyone should sell whatever product they want to sell for whatever price they want to sell it for, but ultimately the market will dictate what it is and people will have to charge less money for everything. Record companies have been overcharging people for way too long and now this is the trouble that they\'re in."', '"Money,Long,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"As soon as I got into music, I tried to be a working, real artist who gets paid for what he does, who doesn\'t have a day job."', '"Music,Day,Real"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I can remember back as far as age 8, performing with the Boston Folk Song Society. It was a Woody Guthrie song."', '"Age,Society,Song"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0c', '"I have always been a singer, a writer, and a musician, not as a prodigy or as in a trade handed to me by my parents, but because of an inner voice or maybe a command from beyond reality as it is usually defined."', '"Reality,Me,Parents"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0d', 'Exploration is really the essence of the human spirit.', '"Travel,Spirit,Human"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0d', 'Capitalism without bankruptcy is like Christianity without hell.', '"Hell,Capitalism,Without"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0d', '"It\'s a vast, lonely, forbidding expanse of nothing rather like clouds and clouds of pumice stone. And it certainly does not appear to be a very inviting place to live or work."', '"Work,Clouds,Stone"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"Boxing is the toughest and loneliest sport in the world. You\'ve got all the fans, lots of hangers-on jumping up and shouting different words. But when you actually go in the ring, it\'s a very lonely and scary place. It\'s just you and the other guy."', '"World,Words,Fans"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"Boxing is a buzz, but I went into it to make a living. I wasn\'t going to go into the ring and get punched in the head for the fun of it."', '"Fun,Living,Go"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"My trainer, George Francis, used to train a lot of African boxers. They\'re hungry guys, man. They\'ve got no trainers, got nothing. They\'re so hungry to do boxing, to make some money."', '"Money,Man,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'Sometimes your dreams come true.', '"Dreams,Your Dreams,True"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'Sometimes when you have bipolar you have days you are grumpy and not feeling yourself.', '"Yourself,Sometimes,Grumpy"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'Boxing is the toughest and loneliest sport in the world.', '"World,Boxing,Sport"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"People take the mickey out of mental health, but it is very delicate."', '"Health,People,Mental Health"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I speak African. I can even speak Italian.', '"Speak,I Can,Even"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"I want to stay healthy, keep fit, eat well, keep a low profile and be a good dad."', '"Good,Dad,Stay"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'Some people like going to the pub; I enjoy going to the gym.', '"People,Enjoy,Some People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I like going to the gym every day.', '"Day,Every Day,Gym"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"But when you actually go in the ring, it\'s a very lonely and scary place. It\'s just you and the other guy."', '"Place,Go,Ring"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I ain\'t got no right to judge someone.', '"Someone,Judge,Right"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"If you\'re not balanced, your mind\'s not balanced... my fuse went."', '"Mind,Your,Balanced"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"When I came into boxing, I brought it to the next level with adverts and doing pantomime and people just got jealous of me doing that."', '"Me,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I wouldn\'t mind getting emotionally involved with a woman.', '"Mind,Woman,Involved"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"Journalists have always written that my mum said that I punched a hole through my cot when I was three years old. I don\'t remember doing that, and I think it was more that I was very energetic."', '"Remember,Doing,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I didn\'t play a great deal of sport in primary school. It was not until I went away to boarding school in Sussex that I really got into sport.', '"Great,School,Play"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"I try and maintain a little bit of fitness, man."', '"Fitness,Man,Try"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'There\'s enough pressure in life without seeking competition. That makes it double pressure.', '"Life,Competition,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"I still get invitations from all over Europe to speak at dinners, and it\'s an honour that promoters and charities can use me to create income."', '"Me,Create,Speak"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"Mental illness is a very powerful thing. If it is with you it is probably going to be there until the day you die. I am trying so hard to break mine, but it is not easy. It is my toughest fight ever."', '"Fight,I Am,Day"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I don\'t normally watch myself on the telly.', '"Myself,Watch,Normally"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I am just working on staying alive.', '"I Am,Alive,Just"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'When you\'re a man you try and be macho.', '"Man,Try,Macho"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'If your brain\'s not right they have good people at the NHS to help you fix it and talk to and counselling to calm you down and to focus you.', '"Good,Focus,Brain"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"My head has got regrets, but I haven\'t."', '"Head,Got,Regrets"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'Being sectioned was the best thing that ever happened to me.', '"Best,Me,Happened"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"Mental illness can happen to anybody. You can be a dustman, a politician, a Tesco worker... anyone. It could be your dad, your brother or your aunt."', '"Dad,Politician,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'People need to have compassion for others.', '"Compassion,People,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', '"If you say you\'ve had a nervous breakdown or things aren\'t right mentally, people run away from you. They think you\'re from \'One Flew Over The Cuckoo\'s Nest,\' you know."', '"People,Know,Nest"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I\'m not really a cutter-off sort of person. I\'ll chat to anybody.', '"Person,Chat,Really"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0e', 'I still believe in marriage.', '"Marriage,Believe,Still"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0f', '"When I was 18, I thought my father was pretty dumb. After a while when I got to be 21, I was amazed to find out how much he\'d learned in three years."', '"Dad,Dumb,Father"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0f', 'A golf course is nothing but a pool room moved outdoors.', '"Nothing,Golf,Pool"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0f', 'Bishops are like umpires. You have to have them to call the close decisions.', '"Decisions,Like,Call"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0f', '"I get a little behind during Lent, but it comes out even at Christmas."', '"Christmas,Behind,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe0f', '"The joy of giving is indeed a pleasure, especially when you get rid of something you don\'t want."', '"Joy,Pleasure,Indeed"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe10', '"If you hang around long enough to show these people what you can do, you have a chance in this acting business."', '"Business,Chance,Long"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe10', '"At 24, my head was as shiny as a cue ball on a billiard table. I naturally thought this meant curtains. Actually, I found it helped. When I was too young to play real character parts, they mistook me for older because of the bald noggin. I got juicy roles right from the start."', '"Character,Me,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"I think sometimes comedians and entertainers and artists, sometimes they get onstage, and it\'s all for what they want to do. I think you still need to do stuff for the audience. They\'re the ones who are making it possible."', '"Sometimes,Possible,Need"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', 'I love John Madden because he makes me feel smart.', '"Love,Me,Smart"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"ESPN has so many characters, it\'s like \'The Simpsons.\'"', '"Like,Many,ESPN"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"I was very stale at Fox. Much of it was my own fault. I was lazy and didn\'t fight for things I wanted to do at other times. Most of my stuff consisted of setup/punchline jokes to the camera - a very old-school approach. I was part of the establishment, I guess."', '"Fight,My Own,Camera"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"ESPN takes itself very seriously, but for some reason, I\'m allowed to be the court jester."', '"Seriously,Reason,Court"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"Fox does the NFL a lot like they program the rest of the network. There\'s sort of a locker room sense of humor that prevails. With ESPN, it\'s more like a pat-you-on-the-back kind of comedy. I mean, they\'ll all get on each other a little bit, but it\'s never mean-spirited."', '"Humor,Rest,Sense Of Humor"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"With Twitter, it\'s a little harder to tell jokes that somebody hasn\'t heard already. You have all these people out there sharing their opinions and telling jokes in real time, and by the time you get on, somebody\'s already done some version of what you\'re trying to do."', '"Time,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', 'I\'m kind of the antithesis of a comedian. People that don\'t like me will agree with that.', '"Me,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe11', '"Most people want to be on TV as much as possible. I went up the ranks so fast because I was doing impressions, and nobody was really doing it when I started. I never got a chance to explore what\'s my comfort level onstage."', '"Chance,People,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"Don\'t follow trends, start trends."', '"Start,Trends,Follow"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', 'I made mistakes in drama. I thought drama was when actors cried. But drama is when the audience cries.', '"Movies,Drama,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"Film is one of the three universal languages, the other two: mathematics and music."', '"Music,Mathematics,Three"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', 'A hunch is creativity trying to tell you something.', '"Imagination,Creativity,Trying"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"If you want to send a message, try Western Union."', '"Try,Want,Message"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"In our film profession you may have Gable\'s looks, Tracy\'s art, Marlene\'s legs or Liz\'s violet eyes, but they don\'t mean a thing without that swinging thing called courage."', '"Courage,Art,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', 'Compassion is a two way street.', '"Street,Compassion,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"Whenever a situation develops to its extreme, it is bound to turn around and become its opposite."', '"Situation,Turn,Opposite"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', '"My advice to young film-makers is this: don\'t follow trends, start them!"', '"Advice,Start,Trends"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe12', 'Scriptwriting is the toughest part of the whole racket... the least understood and the least noticed.', '"Understood,Least,Whole"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'Intelligence is not a science.', '"Science,Intelligence"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'And I argued with that intelligence estimate and I think it is a responsibility of policymakers to use their best judgment on the basis of the intelligence they\'ve received.', '"Best,Intelligence,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"Putin has a lot at stake here and restoring the relationship with the United States, and there are already signs as Sandy mentioned that he\'s moving in the right direction to begin to ascertain that their trade with Iran is not used for the production of nuclear weapons."', '"Relationship,Direction,Moving"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"Of course, China is a key to the North Korea if we\'re going to solve that riddle, but they could also be helpful on Iraq, which is why it\'s important that we maintain a constructive dialogue with China."', '"Important,Why,Dialogue"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'The budget evolved from a management tool into an obstacle to management.', '"Management,Budget,Tool"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"We would like to have friendly regimes with enough broad participation of their populations to maintain long-term stability, so that we would have not only access to the region\'s wealth, but we would be able to ensure the security of our good friend Israel."', '"Good,Wealth,Security"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'We went into Iraq because Iraq posed a threat to the stability of the region and was engaged in the process of trying to develop weapons of mass destruction and had links to terrorists.', '"Process,Trying,Stability"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"These are all elements, but the main thing we can do in the Middle East is encourage the reformist elements."', '"Middle,Middle East,Elements"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'There\'s clearly something to be said for success and following through on your commitments.', '"Success,Your,Through"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'The Crown Prince has said he needs to broaden political participation in the governing of Saudi Arabia.', '"Political,Crown,Needs"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"So, I think even in Saudi Arabia there is movement. And we have to remember that over the years they\'ve stabilized the oil price and that is tremendously important for the economies of the world. I think we have no choice but to work with the government of Saudi Arabia."', '"Work,Government,World"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'Policymakers have to make judgments based on the best intelligence they get.', '"Best,Intelligence,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"Over a period of time, I think the popular will in Iran will prevail."', '"Time,Will,Prevail"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"My understanding is that what was provided was general order of battle information, not operational intelligence. I certainly have no knowledge of US participation in preparing battle and strike packages and doubt strongly that that occurred."', '"Knowledge,Intelligence,Battle"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"Look at what the Omar of Qatar is doing, for example - the King of Morocco, Jordan, Bahrain. There are reform movements taking place, efforts to broaden the political participation of the populations of the region."', '"King,Political,Look"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"It took us 50 months in Germany, post World War II to go from the end of the war to a national election."', '"War,World,Election"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', 'I wouldn\'t even know - and I spent three years in the CIA - I wouldn\'t even know how you\'d start a covert action program in a place like Iran. It would be extraordinarily difficult.', '"Action,Difficult,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"I think the real target of al-Qaeda is Saudi Arabia by the way. They hate us and we\'re a vehicle to get at Saudi Arabia. I think Osama bin Laden really wants to topple that regime and have his people move in, but that\'s a whole other story."', '"Hate,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"I can remember when I was National Security Adviser, the intelligence community told us... they put out an intelligence report saying that Iran would never back off from attacks on shipping in the Gulf if we use force."', '"Intelligence,Community,Remember"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"But at the same time, I think we recognize we can\'t impose democracy from without, particularly American-style democracy. We need to work with those elements in the region that are moving towards a reformed process and there are a number of them."', '"Work,Time,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe13', '"And we ought to work our diplomacy first and I think it\'s a reason it\'s going to respond increasingly to our diplomacy particularly with the president\'s direct involvement in the peace process, and I think that\'s extraordinarily important."', '"Work,Peace,Process"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"My wife said to me: \'If you won the lottery, would you still love me?\' I said: \'Of course I would. I\'d miss you, but I\'d still love you.\'"', '"Love,Wife,Me"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', 'Most of my jokes are racist - usually about the Irish.', '"Jokes,About,Irish"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"I don\'t think my wife likes me very much, when I had a heart attack she wrote for an ambulance."', '"Marriage,Heart,Wife"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', 'What\'s the difference between my wife and a terrorist? You can negotiate with a terrorist.', '"Wife,Difference,Terrorist"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"People in Northern Ireland vote for their church, they don\'t vote with their heads; it is ridiculous."', '"People,Church,Vote"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"So I rang up British Telecom, I said \'I want to report a nuisance caller\', he said \'Not you again\'."', '"Want,Up,British"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"The thirties were troublesome in Belfast, and then of course there was no work for people, and it was terribly religiously divided."', '"Work,People,No Work"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"America has only 100 Senators for 309 million people, but Stormont has 108 members for 1.7 million."', '"America,People,Only"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', 'Have you heard about the Irishman who reversed into a car boot sale and sold the engine?', '"Car,Engine,Who"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"I am accusing him of stealing my best material, he was a very funny man."', '"Funny,Best,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"It\'s never occurred to me to worry about my health, or that I\'ll get old, or that people will stop laughing at me."', '"Health,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe14', '"My idea for peace in the Middle East is to go back to the 1966 line, but to build even more houses for the Palestinians, who are a poor people."', '"Peace,People,Back"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe15', '"All wars come to an end, at least temporarily. But the authority acquired by the state hangs on; political power never abdicates."', '"Power,Political,End"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe15', '"When people say \'let\'s do something about it\', they mean \'let\'s get hold of the political machinery so that we can do something to somebody else.\' And that somebody is invariably you."', '"Political,People,Mean"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe15', 'The pertinent question: if Americans did not want these wars should they have been compelled to fight them?', '"Fight,Want,Question"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe15', 'The State acquires power... and because of its insatiable lust for power it is incapable of giving up any of it. The State never abdicates.', '"Power,Lust,Never"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe16', '"In examining the CIA\'s past and present use of the U.S. media, the Committee finds two reasons for concern. The first is the potential, inherent in covert media operations, for manipulating or incidentally misleading the American public."', '"Past,Media,American"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe16', 'The second is the damage to the credibility and independence of a free press which may be caused by covert relationships with the U.S. journalists and media organizations.', '"Independence,Free,Media"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"You may be deceived if you trust too much, but you will live in torment if you don\'t trust enough."', '"Trust,Live,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', 'A friend is someone with whom you dare to be yourself.', '"Be Yourself,Yourself,Dare"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', 'What is a friend? I will tell you... it is someone with whom you dare to be yourself.', '"Be Yourself,Yourself,Will"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"Most of the things we decide are not what we know to be the best. We say yes, merely because we are driven into a corner and must say something."', '"Best,Know,Corner"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"Responsibility is the thing people dread most of all. Yet it is the one thing in the world that develops us, gives us manhood or womanhood fiber."', '"World,Responsibility,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"You do not succeed because you do not know what you want, but because you don\'t want it intensely enough."', '"Know,Enough,Succeed"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', 'A good motto is: use friendliness but do not use your friends.', '"Good,Motto,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', 'Your sole contribution to the sum of things is yourself.', '"Yourself,Your,Things"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"You are wise, witty and wonderful, but you spend too much time reading this sort of stuff."', '"Time,Wise,Too Much"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', '"Next, in importance to books are their titles."', '"Next,Importance,Titles"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe17', 'Habits are safer than rules; you don\'t have to watch them. And you don\'t have to keep them either. They keep you.', '"Rules,Watch,Keep"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"Young men and young women, full of courage, originality, and genius, are everywhere to be met with."', '"Courage,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"Let us instance one respect in which American life has recently undergone a great change. We allude to its increased devotion to pleasure, to happiness, to dancing, to sport... to the delights of the country, to laughter, and to all forms of cheerfulness."', '"Life,Happiness,Change"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"For women, we intend to do something in a noble and missionary spirit... We mean to appeal to their intellects... and we hereby announce ourselves as determined and bigoted feminists."', '"Women,Spirit,Noble"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"What Marie Antoinette was to eighteenth-century France, Mary Pickford is to twentieth-century America."', '"America,Mary,France"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"In my day, when you called on a girl, her mother was always hollering down to see if she was still unraped, the maid would look in, her father would shuffle his feet in another room. Today the boy calls up, says, \'Meet you at the back door of Stern\'s.\'"', '"Today,Look,Feet"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"My sense of loneliness was not particularly great until I reached sixty. From that time on, I would have given an ex-king\'s ransom if I had been able, in my youth to seduce a lady into thinking of me as a handyman and provider around the house."', '"Time,Great,Youth"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"I have never collected an object or figure from Africa or Oceania because of anything curious about it or because of its utility or historic interest. Everything has been chosen entirely because of its aesthetic significance; its form, feeling, structure, and plastic values."', '"Aesthetic,Never,Curious"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"My interest in society - at times so pronounced that the word \'snob\' comes a little to mind - derives from the fact that I like an immense number of things which society, money, and position bring in their train: painting, tapestries, rare books, smart dresses, dances, gardens, country houses, correct cuisine, and pretty women."', '"Women,Money,Society"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe18', '"We Americans are mildly interested, of course, in reading about the discovery of radium by Madame Curie, but what we really yearn to know is the name of the uncommemorated French female who first mixed a sauce bearnaise."', '"Name,Know,Discovery"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', '"I\'d like to walk into a room sometime and be introduced as the author of something other than that play. There\'s always one thing in a career that has more impact than anything else. In my case, \'The Subject Was Roses\' was that thing."', '"Walk,Roses,Impact"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', 'I remember how I would wait for a play idea. I wasted a tremendous amount of time. I didn\'t realize that ideas could be made into movies or novels.', '"Time,Movies,Wait"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', '"I don\'t believe in updating. If a play works, it draws something from being true to its time."', '"Time,Believe,True"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', '"You reach a time... when fact and fiction blend seamlessly. If you do it too soon, it\'s journalism. If you do it too late, you forget, and it\'s fantasy. There\'s an optimum time."', '"Time,Journalism,Late"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', '"Young men who have been away, been to war, they are different when they come home."', '"War,Men,Home"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', '"The way plays happen, at least with me, it\'s spontaneous combustion of things you\'ve had in your head."', '"Me,Way,Your"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', 'I think of myself as a storyteller.', '"Myself,Think,I Think"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe19', 'You\'re looking at a guy who has no reason to complain about anything.', '"Looking,Anything,Reason"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"Time is money, especially when you are talking to a lawyer or buying a commercial."', '"Money,Time,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"Blessed is he who talks in circles, for he shall become a big wheel."', '"Blessed,Big,Wheel"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'A liberal is a man who will give away everything he doesn\'t own.', '"Man,Will,Everything"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'Get all the fools on your side and you can be elected to anything.', '"Anything,Your,Side"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"Ignorance is never out of style. It was in fashion yesterday, it is the rage today and it will set the pace tomorrow."', '"Today,Tomorrow,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'The way to a woman\'s heart is through your wallet.', '"Heart,Woman,Way"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'A conservative is a fellow who thinks a rich man should have a square deal.', '"Man,Rich,Conservative"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'Life is strange. Every so often a good man wins.', '"Life,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"Rome had Senators too, that\'s why it declined."', '"Why,Rome,Senators"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"Some have greatness thrust upon them, but not lately."', '"Greatness,Some,Thrust"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'Preachers denounce sin as if it was available to everyone.', '"Sin,Everyone,Available"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'The news of any politician\'s death should be listed under \'Public Improvements.\'', '"Death,News,Politician"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'It is not necessary to have enemies if you go out of your way to make friends hate you.', '"Hate,Way,Enemies"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', '"In polite society one laughs at all the jokes, including the ones one has heard before."', '"Society,Jokes,Heard"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1a', 'Nothing annoys a woman more than to have company drop in unexpectedly and find the house looking as it usually does.', '"Woman,Looking,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"One of my favorite movies of all time is \'It\'s A Wonderful Life,\' which is a pretty interesting choice for a seasonal Christmas favorite, because it\'s about a guy who wants to commit suicide and is presented with reasons not to."', '"Life,Time,Movies"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'Visual storytelling of one kind or another has been around since cavemen were drawing on the walls.', '"Drawing,Walls,Storytelling"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"The human race is fundamentally insane. If you put two of us into a room together, we\'re soon gonna start figuring out good reasons to kill one another."', '"Good,Together,Start"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '\'The Exorcist\' is amazing because it recognizes that silences can be as powerful as sound effects.', '"Amazing,Sound,Because"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"And I don\'t think I\'m giving away any secrets here, but there are a lot of terrible scripts in this town."', '"Secrets,Terrible,Away"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'I am fascinated with times past.', '"I Am,Past,Am"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"A director shouldn\'t get in the way of the movie, the story should."', '"Way,Story,Get"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'I think once you\'ve finished a movie you really have to detach from it so that you can come back and watch it as an audience member.', '"Back,Audience,Come"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'Some of us have great original ideas and some of us depend on adaptations.', '"Great,Ideas,Us"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"To me, length is an artificial and arbitrary factor in a film."', '"Me,Film,Artificial"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'I think a story should take as long to tell as it is appropriate to that particular story.', '"Long,Story,Tell"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"Boy, I\'d hate to shoot on tape or disc or whatever the hell they\'re talking about. I love film."', '"Love,Hate,Hell"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', '"The only person who can, with impunity, make the movie he wants to make, has got to be Steven Spielberg."', '"Person,Only,He"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'Stanley Kubrick was a big inspiration. People accuse me of never using my own material. But when did Kubrick? You look at his films and they are completely unique... completely separate entities.', '"Look,Me,Unique"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'I\'d like to think that my films are personal enough to exist without hearkening back to their respective novels.', '"Back,Enough,Personal"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1b', 'I spent 20 years of my career primarily being a writer for hire.', '"Being,Career,Hire"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Thank you for listening. Thank you for abiding me. And now, ladies and gentlemen, boys and girls, children of all ages, I bid you goodbye and take my leave."', '"Me,Children,Listening"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Pete Rose may not make the Hall of Fame, but a statue of him is going to be erected outside the Cincinnati Reds ballpark."', '"Fame,Outside,Statue"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Despite the fact that every sport this side of badminton worries about concussions that result in brain damage, CTE, the National Hockey League refuses to accept the overwhelming medical science. Good grief - the NHL still permits fights."', '"Science,Good,Medical"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Majesty is a thing of beauty to behold, whatever the particular enterprise."', '"Beauty,Whatever,Behold"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"On Monument Avenue in Richmond, Va., there are statues of five Confederate luminaries and then, incongruously in this company, one of Arthur Ashe."', '"Company,Five,Then"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"We start 2016 with a command: that the subject of Pete Rose and the Hall of Fame is over, finis, kaput forever and ever. As sure as we will no longer discuss whether Lindsey Graham or George Pataki can be president."', '"Start,Will,Fame"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Once again it is peaceful at Augusta National Golf Club, after some rather ugly stand-offs in recent years, when the club balked at changing its all-white, all-male membership tradition. African-Americans and female Americans are on the club manifest now along with other golf-Americans, and all is serene once again."', '"Ugly,Golf,Tradition"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think the best thing I\'ve written is a story called \'The Boxer and the Blonde.\' It\'s a piece about Billy Conn, the white would-be heavyweight champion of the world, who lived in Pittsburgh."', '"Best,World,Champion"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"She glances at the photo, and the pilot light of memory flickers in her eyes."', '"Eyes,Light,Memory"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"In days of yore, Opening Day of the baseball season was special, signifying that spring had come at last. Today, however, Opening Day sort of dribbles into existence, and the spiritual start of spring now belongs to the Masters golf tournament, where the azaleas and magnolias and dogwood bloom."', '"Today,Day,Spiritual"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'All sorts of famous sports people have been suspended for extended periods.', '"Sports,Famous,People"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"People often lump radio and television together because they are both broadcast mediums. But radio, anyway, and the radio I do for NPR, is much closer to writing than it is to television."', '"Together,People,Television"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'The only thing we know for sure about superiority in sports in the United States of America in the 20th century is that Bill Russell and the Boston Celtics teams he led stand alone as the ultimate winners.', '"Alone,Sports,America"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"It was not that long ago when the accepted wisdom in football was that the running game had to be established - that was always the obligatory verb: established - before passes could become effective. My, we know how that has changed. Now the pass is established from the get-go, and running is an afterthought."', '"Wisdom,Football,Game"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"It\'s almost impossible to explain how little the NBA amounted to when I started covering it in 1963. It wasn\'t fair to call it bush, although everybody did. It was simply small - only nine teams - and insignificant."', '"Impossible,Small,Explain"', '2023-05-29 11:59:00', '2023-05-29 11:59:00'),
	('397269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Quickness and momentum. You take the whole last generation of sports, listening to them, even reading about them, watching the games, analyzing them, arguing about them, instant-replaying them, second-guessing them, and all you\'ll distill from them is quickness and momentum."', '"Sports,Generation,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Dan Rather pulling on a sweater and thereby winning a whole new chunk of the populace: That\'s television. President Reagan\'s press conferences: That\'s television. Keith Jackson is television. So are Kermit the Frog, instant replay, and the Fiesta Bowl."', '"Winning,New,Frog"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"We exalted that Michael Phelps-consecrated water. Rose petals were strewn in Peyton Manning\'s path when he retired. But hey, that\'s natural. As we should, we admire those in any craft, no less so in sports, who appear out of nowhere to achieve remarkable feats."', '"Sports,Water,Path"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"So much about big-time college sports is criticized. But the worst scandal is almost never mentioned: the academic fraud wherein the student-athletes, so-called, are admitted without even remotely adequate credentials and then aren\'t educated so much as they are just kept eligible."', '"Sports,Fraud,Worst"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"ESPN is all meat and potatoes. It\'s pretty much scouting reports. There isn\'t a great deal of humor, and when there is, it\'s pretty sophomoric."', '"Humor,Great,Meat"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"That\'s the greatest compliment I can get: when somebody from Key West says, \'Hey, Bubba.\' That means I\'m in!"', '"I Can,Compliment,Key"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"By coincidence, this particular tiny show on earth that consists entirely of me talking about sports on NPR is also folding its tent flaps this May of 2017. Yes, this is my swansong, my farewell, my last hurrah. Adieu, adios, arrivederci, auf wiedersehen."', '"Sports,Me,Earth"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Remember when John Roberts was seeking confirmation of the Supreme Court, and he said judges should be just like umpires, just calling balls and strikes? Well, turnabout is fair play. What baseball needs behind the plate are umpires like those judges who are called strict constructionists, which means you follow subtle law to the letter."', '"Law,Remember,Follow"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"It\'s interesting too, that the coach of that Georgia Tech team who led his valiant warriors to those 222 points was none other than John Heisman. Yes, he whom the Heisman trophy is named for, an award that honors that college player who best exemplifies excellence and integrity."', '"Best,Integrity,Award"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Don\'t dismiss Auriemma and UConn just because their excellence shines on the female side of the coin.', '"Excellence,Just Because,Coin"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Every now and then, I get a free ticket from someone, and I look at the price, and it says $800, and I\'m thinking, \'A thousand dollars to see,\' I said, \'There\'s no ballgame in the world worth that kind of money,\' and yet the attendance for sports is more than it ever has been."', '"Money,Sports,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Bill Russell was the pivot on which the whole sport turned.', '"Whole,Sport,Which"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think there are more good sportswriters doing more good sportswriting than ever before. But I also believe that the one thing that\'s largely gone out is what made sport such fertile literary territory - the characters, the tales, the humor, the pain, what Hollywood calls \'the arc.\'"', '"Good,Humor,Pain"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Several NBA teams got their best gates every season when they scheduled a doubleheader and booked the Globetrotters and their stooges for the opening game.', '"Best,Game,Opening"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'You can tell all you need to about a society from how it treats animals and beaches.', '"Society,Tell,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I am something of a ham. Yeah, I\'d always been a writer. But in high school, I acted in plays. So it wasn\'t as if you had to drag the words out of my vocal chords."', '"I Am,Words,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"If I come on three days after the Super Bowl and say pretty much what everybody else has said, what\'s the point? That was the tricky thing... coming up with a new angle every time - or most times, because you couldn\'t bat a thousand."', '"Time,New,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"If I\'d grown up in Sao Paulo, I\'m sure I would\'ve been a great soccer fan."', '"Great,Fan,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I don\'t think there are many kids who sit around and want to be actors. I don\'t think there are many kids who want to sit around and want to be senators. But so many of us want to be athletes, so we\'re envious of them, and we put them up on that pedestal."', '"Sit,Us,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think we have enough trouble finding community in this country, and sport does provide that. It is a mediocrisy, the greatest mediocrisy. If you\'re the best, it shows in sports. Nobody can say, \'Well, he\'s only there because of his connections,\' or whatever. In that sense, I suppose it upholds democracy and the best in us."', '"Best,Sports,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I remember, when I was growing up in Baltimore, we\'d get on a streetcar and go down to see the Orioles, and for a couple of bucks, you could get a pretty good seat. Kids can\'t do that anymore. So I think that changes the whole nature of sports."', '"Nature,Good,Sports"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I have survived so long because I\'ve been blessed with talented and gracious colleagues and with a top brass who let me choose my topics every week and then allowed me to express opinions that were not always popular. Well, someone had to stand up to the yackety-yak soccer cult."', '"Colleagues,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I\'ve been delivering these little homilies since 1980 - that\'s 37 years - and altogether, NPR statisticians tell me, my bloviation total is 1,656 commentaries - and I trust you\'ve hung onto every word."', '"Trust,Me,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Johnny U was an American original, a piece of work like none other, excepting maybe Paul Bunyan and Horatio Alger."', '"Work,American,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Nowadays, of course, flesh peddlers and scouting services identify the best athletes when they are still in junior high. Prospects are not allowed to sneak up on us."', '"Best,Us,High"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Before the Colts arrived in 1947, the best athlete in town was a woman duckpin bowler named Toots Barger. Football? The biggest games in Baltimore had been when Johns Hopkins took on Susquehanna or Franklin & Marshall at homecoming."', '"Best,Football,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I never saw war, so that is still my vision of manhood: Unitas standing courageously in the pocket, his left arm flung out in a diagonal to the upper deck, his right cocked for the business of passing, down amidst the mortals. Lock and load."', '"War,Business,Vision"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'I think I would die if I couldn\'t get to the typewriter every day. I really need that.', '"Day,Die,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"There are some books that get huge numbers of positive reviews, but reading them satiates people. They say, \'I\'ve read enough now\'."', '"Positive,People,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'I\'ll forever be grateful to NPR that they gave me such extraordinary freedom... It was 37 years of a fond relationship.', '"Freedom,Relationship,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Nothing made me happier than to hear from literally hundreds of listeners who would tell me how much the commentaries revealed about a subject they otherwise had never cared much for.', '"Me,Nothing,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Sport is an art: it has incredible appeal everywhere on this earth, and it fills so many human hearts with passion that it\'s impossible to dismiss."', '"Art,Passion,Impossible"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The wonderful thing about delivering sports commentary on NPR was that because it has such a broad audience, I was able to reach people who otherwise had little or no interest in sport - especially as an important part of our human culture."', '"Sports,Culture,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The dollar is a winner. The euro is a tie. Get off the dime, Europe, and play to win."', '"Winner,Win,Europe"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The hardest thing in the world is to write something critical about someone and then show up the next day in the locker room. I mean, that is not fun, and that takes an awful lot of guts. And I never enjoyed that."', '"World,Fun,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I remember one time I wrote something very, very critical about Wilt Chamberlain. The next time I saw him - and Wilt was not a man, as huge as he was - he was not a man of confrontation. And we were in the Lakers locker room. And he sent Jerry West over, and he said, \'Frank, Wilt would like you to leave.\'"', '"Time,Man,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"When I was covering games, and this is back in the \'60s, you\'d go into the manager\'s office. I can still visualize Earl Weaver from the Baltimore Orioles. I can just see Earl now in his underwear... with a beer in one hand and a cigarette in the other, holding court. And that was the way it was done then."', '"Way,Beer,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"What we accepted as great art - whether the book, the script, the painting, the symphony - is that which could be saved and savored. But the performances of the athletic artists who ran and jumped and wrestled were gone with the wind."', '"Art,Great,Wind"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"How did females become \'guys?\' How did everyone become \'guys?\' Remember, too, that a male guy was something of a scoundrel. And a wise guy was a fresh kid, a whippersnapper. In its most other famous evocation, men in Brooklyn said \'youse guys.\' Damon Runyon referred to hustlers, gamblers, and other nefarious types as guys."', '"Men,Famous,Wise"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Football teams represent cities and colleges and schools. The people have built great stadiums, and the game is culturally intertwined with our calendar. We don\'t go back to college for the college. We go back for a football game, and, yes, we even call that \'homecoming.\'"', '"Great,Football,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"You have to do what the market requires of you... You either keep swimming, or you sink."', '"Swimming,Keep,Market"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"NPR allowed me to treat sports seriously, as another branch on the tree of culture."', '"Sports,Culture,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"You\'re writing about young, vibrant people; there are wins and losses. In other words, it\'s great drama."', '"Great,Words,Drama"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think, in accepting the amount of money that athletes make, I think that fans accept that now. It\'s the nature of the beast; that\'s the way it is, so they understand it. All, I think, fans have changed - because the price of tickets has gone up so much - that they feel a certain sense of entitlement when they go to a game."', '"Nature,Money,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"To write long pieces - or not even long pieces - to write stuff like the columns of Red Smith and people like that - they\'re different then what it is today. Everything today is based on x\'s and o\'s. Inside baseball, it\'s all, \'Who\'s gonna win?\' or you\'re comparing things - it\'s not as thoughtful as it used to be."', '"Today,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"To compare writing an article for \'Sports Illustrated\' to doing a piece for \'Real Sports\', the article, it was all me. You know, I\'m out there by myself with my pad and pencil. \'Real Sports,\' I\'ve got a producer, an assistant producer, and cameramen. It\'s an individual game versus a team game."', '"Sports,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The Masters is not greedy. You wanna buy a Masters souvenir logo shirt? Sure, let\'s go over to the nearest Ralph Lauren boutique. Oops, you can only purchase Masters memorabilia at the Masters, this one week of the year."', '"Shirt,Week,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Yes, the Masters is too stylish to be an American icon. It\'s as out of character for Uncle Sam as a McDonald\'s is for France."', '"Character,American,Stylish"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'The strike zone should be what the rule book says it is and not a personal idiosyncrasy.', '"Personal,Book,Strike"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"If there ever was an \'America\'s team,\' it would be itty-bitty, little Green Bay, stuck way up there somewhere, owned by the salt-of-the-Earth citizens themselves."', '"Green,America,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'The Cowboys were never America\'s team any more than Anthony Weiner was America\'s congressman.', '"America,Never,More"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'It\'s still the tradition for various football powerhouses to pay guarantees to schools with cream-puff teams to come on over to our place and submit to massacre.', '"Football,Place,Tradition"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"As it happens, Cumberland was on the verge of bankruptcy and had to give up football. But the villainous Heisman made it play a game that had been scheduled when Cumberland still had a team, or Heisman threatened to demand a $3,000 forfeiture fee that could well have put the school out of existence."', '"Football,Game,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Since too few Americans go to the polls, I say what this country needs is a bobblehead election, where voters will get free bobblehead dolls of their choice when they show up and vote for president."', '"Free,Choice,Election"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think the four major leagues ought to set up a joint commission - say, of retired judges - to rule on athletes who are accused of doing bad things away from the game. Then each league would retain its independence in determining what penalties their players should get for infractions committed within the sport."', '"Independence,Game,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"In the television era, the second week of the Olympics is reserved for what is considered the marquee event: track and field."', '"Television,Week,Field"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"While swimming was always a spotlight sport, I was, if you will, sort of present at the creation when gymnastics became the new star lead-off hitter."', '"Swimming,New,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Statues of sports stars are all the rage - especially in baseball.', '"Sports,Stars,Baseball"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"It\'s fascinating, isn\'t it, that whereas so many of our statues have been of military leaders, now it may well be sports stars who are the ones more likely to be so honored."', '"Sports,Stars,Honored"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Does each of us need to suffer agony to understand how brutal our gridiron entertainment is? Surely, seeing is believing enough. So, what is football doing to us as a people? How do we explain an America that alone in the world so loves this savage sport?"', '"Alone,Football,World"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"At all levels - with men and women - the 3-point shot has utterly transformed the way the game is played. More and more, the players are spread out, looking to pop behind the 3-point arc."', '"Women,Men,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"More and more teams are, in the vernacular, \'going small,\' with only one big man down deep. Good grief, the position of power forward is in the process of going the way of short shorts."', '"Good,Power,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', 'Owners own teams so that they might move them to another municipality with better luxury boxes.', '"Better,Own,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The Tigers, Lions, Red Wings, and Pistons are there today as sure as they were when what was good for General Motors was good for the country. Would you rather have a basketball team, or would you rather be Detroit?"', '"Good,Today,Wings"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I do honestly believe that, in the 21st century, sport is the most significant cultural element in this imperfect world. It calls for serious attention."', '"Believe,World,Serious"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I get very envious of my general news colleagues who are always being handed sexy new stuff like global warming, China, and Donald Trump, while my sports colleagues and I must be eternally satisfied with the same old home-court advantage, soccer, and momentum."', '"Sports,Sexy,Colleagues"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"When Juan Antonio Samaranch said the Olympics are more important than the Catholic Church, I just couldn\'t believe it. I said to myself, \'Don\'t let your expression show that he has just made a total ass of himself. Be cool, and just keep right on talking.\'"', '"Cool,Myself,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I think every time I can find a story that touches that human nerve, and even sometimes makes you cry, I think that I\'ve found something that I\'ll like very much."', '"Time,Sometimes,Cry"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"If you\'re a father of a child who dies, it\'s an experience that never leaves you. It scars you forever and ever and ever. And so when I do any kind of story with somebody who\'s in the same position as my daughter was, there\'s no question that something comes out of me and embraces that story in a way that only a father who lost a child could."', '"Experience,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Because I lost a daughter, eight years old, to cystic fibrosis, I think that anytime that I\'m dealing with people who, like Andrea Yeager, are trying to help those sick children, I identify very much with them."', '"Lost,Children,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"You can stand at a bar and scream all you want about who was the greatest athlete and which was the greatest sports dynasty, and you can shout out your precious statistics, and maybe you\'re right, and maybe the red-faced guy down the bar - the one with the foam on his beer and the fancy computer rankings - is right, but nobody really knows."', '"Sports,Statistics,Beer"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The year after Russell retired, in the famous seventh game of the NBA Finals at Madison Square Garden, Willis Reed, the New York Knicks center, limped onto the court against the Los Angeles Lakers, inspiring his team and freezing Chamberlain into a benign perplexity."', '"Famous,Game,New"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"First and foremost, Howard Cosell is sports. There are all these people, these fans, who claim that when Cosell does a game on television, they turn off the sound on the TV and listen to the radio broadcast. Oh, sure. You probably know critics in your neighborhood who vow the same thing. Well, too bad for them."', '"Sports,Game,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '\'Good Morning America\' is television to a fare-thee-well.', '"Good,Morning,America"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The stories that are most unfamiliar, the ones that seem to come out of the blue about people that aren\'t well known, usually come from producers that have really done a lot of homework and looked around. Other stories come from the correspondents."', '"Blue,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I\'m a writer. I\'m moonlighting on television. I never made any pretensions to that. As much as I like being on \'Real Sports,\' I have been a writer since I was a little boy, and that\'s still my first love."', '"Love,Sports,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"It costs a lot of money to deliver newsprint. It\'s so much easier to do it through the air, Internet, radio, television. The second easiest thing is to do it through the mail. But when you have to take something heavy and put it on someone\'s doorstep, that costs a lot of money."', '"Money,Internet,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"There were a lot of places, including Los Angeles, that didn\'t have major league baseball. There were other really large cities that had no major league teams, but at least they had college football."', '"Football,Baseball,Places"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I can remember going to see the minor league Orioles. Until I was 15 years old, we\'d go down with 3,000 people to watch them play the Syracuse Chiefs or the Jersey City Little Giants. That\'s what passed for Baltimore sports."', '"Sports,City,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"In the summer of 1963, my second with \'Sports Illustrated,\' Jerry Tax, the basketball editor, got the Celtics\' Frank Ramsey, the NBA\'s first famous sixth man, to do a piece for the magazine revealing some of the devious little tricks of his trade. Things like surreptitiously holding an opponent\'s shorts - nickel-and-dime stuff."', '"Sports,Famous,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"The NBA Schedule was made up by one man, Eddie Gottlieb, who had owned the Philadelphia Warriors. Eddie had a Buddha-like body and a crinkly smile, and because he had also been an owner in baseball\'s old Negro leagues, he was known as the Mogul."', '"Smile,Man,Body"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"I had gone to work for \'Newsweek\', left \'Newsweek\' and went to work for \'Vanity Fair,\' and then went back to \'Newsweek\'. I came back to \'SI\' as a contract writer."', '"Work,Back,Contract"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"Hard as it is to believe, there were three magazines fighting over me. \'Newsweek\' wanted to keep me, \'ESPN The Magazine\' was coming into existence and wanted me, and \'SI\' wanted to bring me back. Isn\'t that amazing? I had a choice, like a free agent."', '"Amazing,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1c', '"\'SI\' came to me and said, \'We want you to do a story on Russell as the greatest team player,\' which I certainly agreed with."', '"Me,Story,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"To understand and reconnect with our stories, the stories of the ancestors, is to build our identities."', '"Ancestors,Understand,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', 'We all belong to an ancient identity. Stories are the rivers that take us there.', '"Identity,Us,Belong"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"First a piece of Irish wisdom: you should always listen to a bookie. For they have a saying, \'Money tells a good story,\' and somewhere in their odds is a kind of science-fiction existentialism that decrees that we, the people, know everything. In other words, betting patterns often make for good, unconscious soothsaying."', '"Wisdom,Money,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"\'The Great Gatsby,\' by F. Scott Fitzgerald, remains the most perfect novel that has ever come out of the United States. Everything in the book moves as it should, in the manner of a piece by Bach or Mozart."', '"Great,Perfect,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', 'Kitchens are for conversation. They\'re not just for cooking; they\'re for conversations.', '"Cooking,Conversation,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"Storytelling, in print or speech, needs vital energy."', '"Energy,Speech,Storytelling"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', 'I\'d have to struggle to find a subject in which I can\'t get some kind of interested pulse started.', '"Struggle,Find,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"Writers have opinions - that, in part, is why they write. Therefore they have strong likes and dislikes."', '"Why,Opinions,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"For a startling period of my life, I reported the Troubles in Ireland for the BBC. I lived in Dublin and was called out to all sorts of incidents that, if taken together, add up to a war - bombings, assassinations, riots, shootings, robberies, jailbreaks, kidnappings, and sieges."', '"Life,War,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"As an arts journalist in London, working mainly for the BBC, I interviewed hundreds if not thousands of authors. From them I gleaned a great deal of passing instruction in writing and I observed one fascinating detail: no two writers approach their work - physically - in the same way."', '"Work,Great,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"If you ever want to understand multitasking in prose, James Joyce is your man."', '"Man,Understand,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"If you have a book, you have a friend."', '"Friend,Book,You"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', '"If you need proof of how the oral relates to the written, consider that many great novelists, including Joyce and Hemingway, never submitted a piece of work without reading it aloud."', '"Work,Great,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1d', 'I write - and then I write some more.', '"More,Then,Some"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'Being homeless is like living in a post-apocalyptic world. You\'re on the outskirts of society.', '"Society,World,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '\'Candida\' was difficult: stimulating but very wordy.', '"Difficult,Very,Stimulating"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"I remember, when they started remaking \'Star Wars,\' the fury that surrounded that whole thing, and, \'How dare they?\' But now, that\'s just a common denominator."', '"Remember,Dare,Surrounded"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'Theatre\'s a whole different beast to film. It requires a lot more of you.', '"Beast,More,Theatre"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'I don\'t know how consciously anyone looks for a father figure.', '"Father,Know,Looks"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"I\'m sure there will come a time when I won\'t be able to, you know, walk around so easy sometimes, or it\'s just things that I don\'t necessarily want. I don\'t really necessarily want to be famous."', '"Time,Famous,Walk"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"The world is ending, make no mistake. It\'s coming to an end. This can\'t go on for much longer. Capitalism has to fall."', '"World,Mistake,Ending"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"We\'re coming to the peak, I think soon, before we have to come back to, like, humanity. Humanity needs to look, and it hasn\'t been looking for so long."', '"Look,Humanity,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'I\'ve had to wean myself away to make sure that any choices I make are grounded in myself rather than the seeking of approval.', '"Myself,Choices,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"You don\'t realize until afterwards that if you feed the subconscious, it will bleed into your everyday life."', '"Life,Will,Realize"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'People are going to keep making stuff. Things are going to be spin-offs.', '"People,Things,Keep"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"My old man, he\'s done it very differently from me. He had years of honing his craft and years of doing all that stuff before he even had to worry about \'Game of Thrones.\' So he\'s absolutely established himself as an actor without the fear of having to have a personality as well."', '"Fear,Personality,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"I had a dream. I dreamed I was on this island, and there were two hotels, and one hotel was filled with dead people, and the other one wasn\'t, and I was in the hotel full of dead people."', '"Hotel,Dead,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"Dialect was my biggest fear. So, I spent a long time working with dialect coaches just trying to get American down. I think it\'s very important and very easy to misinterpret."', '"Time,Fear,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'I don\'t drive.', 'Drive', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"My father is such an amazing, beautiful actor. He\'s incredible, and he helps me a lot."', '"Amazing,Beautiful,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', 'Harry Potter was my first job.', '"Job,First,First Job"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1e', '"Although I grew up around movies, I don\'t know that I assumed I was going to be an actor."', '"Movies,Know,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'All businessmen are scum.', 'Businessmen', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', '"I am not against Muslim schools. But as I believe in integration, I think we would be better off overall if we did not have denominational schools at all."', '"Believe,I Am,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'There are alternate definitions of manhood in the West.', '"Manhood,Definitions,Alternate"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'I don\'t think we can go into important local elections next year... with Tony Blair as leader and expect to keep many of the councillors we\'ve got now.', '"Important,Go,Next"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'The present system of protecting NHS patients was a bit of a shambles.', '"Present,System,NHS"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'Smoking is the now the principal avoidable cause of premature death in Britain. It hits the worst off people hardest of all. Smoking is one of the principal causes of the health gap which leads to poorer people being ill more often and dying sooner.', '"Health,Death,Smoking"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', 'I think I\'ve had a very privileged life.', '"Life,Think,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', '"My own view is that if you filled every member of the parliamentary Labour party with a truth drug and lashed them to a polygraph lie detector, very, very few of them would support foundation hospitals."', '"Truth,View,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', '"If you say someone is thrilled, it implies talk of an exciting project. I\'m wary of such talk."', '"Talk,Project,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe1f', '"It is more important for Labour to raise the reputation of politics than for the Tories, who are only in politics for the money."', '"Politics,Money,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"If you\'re sending a message to extraterrestrials, what you want to send is what\'s special about us and our planet - what is unusual. Now, that\'s not basic chemistry or mineralogy; it\'s pretty much the cultural stuff and the consequences of evolution."', '"Chemistry,Evolution,Special"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"The story seems to be that almost every star has a planetary system... and, also, the definition of \'habitable zone\' has expanded. In our system, it used to be that only Mars and Earth were potentially habitable. Now we\'ve got an ocean on Europa... Titan."', '"Earth,Story,Ocean"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"There was a magic about pulsars... no other things in the sky had such labels on them. Each one had its own distinct pulsing frequency, so it could be identified by anybody, including other creatures, after a long period of time and far, far away."', '"Time,Sky,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"In 1957, I was studying the Pleiades star cluster at Harvard University\'s radio observatory. On one occasion, we saw an added feature in the data. It turned out to be an amateur radio enthusiast near the observatory, but at the time, I thought we had detected clear evidence of another civilisation."', '"Time,Data,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"We send messages all the time, free of charge. There\'s a big shell out there now, 80 light-years around us. A civilization only a little more advanced than we are can pick those things up."', '"Time,Free,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"Right now, there could well be messages from the stars flying right through this room. Through you and me. And if we had the right receiver set up properly, we could detect them. I still get chills thinking about it."', '"Thinking,Stars,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', 'The pulsar map is not dangerous at all. It will likely never even be seen by extraterrestrials.', '"Will,Never,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', 'Nature never uses prime numbers. But mathematicians do.', '"Nature,Numbers,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"It now appears that essentially every star has a planetary system. In the very beginning, we thought at best half."', '"Best,Beginning,Half"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"No company is hiring anyone to search for messages from aliens. Most people don\'t seem to think there\'s much benefit to it. The lack of interest is, I think, because most people don\'t realize what even a simple detection would really mean."', '"Simple,Search,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"While NASA talks about \'Are we alone?\' as a number one question, they are putting zero money into searching for intelligent life. There\'s a big disconnect there."', '"Life,Alone,Money"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe20', '"People presume we\'ve been somehow monitoring the entire sky at all frequencies, all the time, but we haven\'t yet been able to do any of those things. The fact is, all the SETI efforts to date have only closely examined a couple thousand nearby stars, and we\'re only just now learning which of those might have promising planets."', '"Time,Learning,Sky"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I was into skateboarding, so through skating I kind of got into hip hop by discovering it through skate videos."', '"Through,Skateboarding,Skating"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"Whether it\'s a huge hit or sold five copies, as long artistically and creatively I can stand by what I did, then I\'ll feel successful."', '"Long,Feel,Stand"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'Internet has created the ability to connect people instantly.', '"Internet,People,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I look at the big picture and try not to create with ego.', '"Look,Picture,Ego"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"The Kingsway Music Library was sort of a byproduct of all the creation I was doing. As creators, we kind of just create blindly sometimes and I couldn\'t physically see every idea through, so I created this ecosystem where I made the ideas available to people to download, to sample and to put their own twist on it."', '"Music,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I wanted to be a great producer so I studied great hip-hop producers, but also stuff beyond that: Phil Spector, David Axelrod, Gamble and Huff. They\'re equally as influential to me as Dilla, Premier, and Pete Rock."', '"Great,Me,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I\'m not one for the limelight I suppose.', '"Limelight,Suppose"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I come from the school of hip-hop where you just buy records and sample records all the time. Doing that is tough sometimes, because if you get a placement on a major record, your record could get shelved because of clearance issues."', '"Time,Tough,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"When I go in the studio with Post, I have a really good idea of what he\'s going to gravitate to, what we can work with."', '"Work,Good,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I make popular music but I\'m not necessarily a pop produce.', '"Music,Make,Pop"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I grew up on hip-hop and crate-digging and those sensibilities are deeply ingrained in me.', '"Me,Hip-Hop,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'The thread that ties together everything I love is honesty in the intention.', '"Love,Love Is,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'You never know what can happen if you get sampled by the biggest artist in the world.', '"World,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I might find out about a songwriter and start following them on Instagram. Within a day, we might be hanging out and feeling out whether we can work together."', '"Work,Together,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I try to create something that draws you in without overthinking it. Something that resonates with you automatically that you don\'t have to think about. That\'s what the best pop is about: Michael Jackson, The Beatles, Nirvana - these guys made some of the most authentic and popular music."', '"Best,Music,Create"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"As I change and grow, different things excite me and I just follow where that leads me."', '"Change,Me,Grow"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I\'m definitely interested by a lot of things outside of music - technology, film, quantum physics - and I\'m realizing that I can put my creativity into anything I kind of choose to."', '"Technology,Music,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"Once \'0 to 100\' happened, it sort of spun this chain reaction - really the first big record that I was a part of. It was a big, life-changing thing for me."', '"Me,Big,First"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I love Nirvana, Weezer and a lot of pop punk stuff - Blink-182, I loved."', '"Love,Loved,Punk"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"Nirvana, Weezer and Smashing Pumpkins, all those bands, at their core, are just really incredible pop music and I think a lot of that stuff has deeply affected the way I approach music."', '"Music,Way,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I can see that everybody has their own challenges that they are dealing with. But what\'s so beautiful about music is that it brings people together, levels the playing field and opens people up."', '"Music,Beautiful,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"If you can make the best music ever but it requires bringing in a few different perspectives, I\'d rather make the best music ever."', '"Best,Music,Rather"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'Broken Clocks\' is actually a song I produced for my boy River Tiber featuring my boy Daniel Caesar.', '"River,Song,Boy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I\'m just at home all the time wearing jogging pants.', '"Time,Home,Jogging"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"My approach to making music has always been making ideas and developing them. Sometimes I develop them all the way by myself. The other part of development is I will work with my friends who are just some of the best producers in the world, give them an idea."', '"Work,Best,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I love music with real instruments. I\'m not one of those guys that\'s a purist about analog vs. digital, but I love the analog approach. Sonically, I connect to that."', '"Love,Music,Digital"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I love the process of collaboration... to me it just makes sense.', '"Love,Me,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I know people who have sampled gospel music, and then they go to clear the sample, and it\'s like, \'You can\'t take the Lord\'s music and make this.\'"', '"Music,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I don\'t really generate material specifically for the Kingsway Music Library. It\'s just a product of the way I work.', '"Work,Music,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"I make so many ideas, it\'s impossible to finish every single one."', '"Impossible,Ideas,Finish"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"When you\'re producing, you\'re really just making a series of decisions."', '"Decisions,Just,Making"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'You can\'t just plug your guitar in your computer and make it sound like an old record.', '"Guitar,Sound,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', 'I totally embrace the different transformations we\'ve seen in hip-hop throughout the years.', '"Hip-Hop,Embrace,Seen"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"In a band everyone plays their part, and I look at production the same way."', '"Look,Way,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe21', '"Kanye is producing in the true sense of the word. \'Real Friends\' was an idea started by me and Boi-1da. We passed it off to Kanye, and Kanye kind of stripped it down and had Havoc add some drums to it. Kanye had the vision. That\'s really true-school production."', '"Vision,Me,True"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe22', 'I hope my work has inspired young artists. I have always tried to maintain my freedom as an artist and I feel it is one of the main reasons I have been successful.', '"Work,Hope,Freedom"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe22', '"When it came to my art, I went my own way and did not follow the trends."', '"Art,Way,Trends"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe22', '"By the time I was a teenager, I knew I wanted to be an artist. I was a born draftsman and liked all forms of art, so I just knew that\'s what I wanted to do."', '"Time,Art,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe22', '"What I do is create images, period."', '"Create,Images,Period"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"The object of China\'s strategy is inexorably to supplant the United States as the world\'s premier economic power, and if necessary, to defeat us militarily."', '"Power,World,Strategy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Boone Pickens should be commended for his leadership on American energy security, and for bringing Ted Turner along on some sensible approaches to enhancing it."', '"Leadership,Energy,Security"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"History demonstrates that previous military drawdowns invited aggression by our enemies. After World War I, America drew down forces until the U.S. Army had fewer than 100,000 men in uniform. That weakness invited Nazi aggression in Europe and the imperial Japanese attack at Pearl Harbor."', '"War,History,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Unfortunately, the cyber threat to \'the grid\' is only one means of eviscerating the soft underbelly of American society. Another which has been getting increasing attention could be delivered via the kind of nuclear-armed ballistic missile that Iran and North Korea have been developing: a strategic electro-magnetic pulse attack."', '"Society,American,Attention"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Unbeknownst to most American investors, significant portions of their public pension, mutual fund, life insurance and private portfolios are comprised of stocks of privately held companies that partner with state sponsors of terror."', '"Life,Partner,American"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"If the area were on or near the U.S. continental shelf, such data could well provide an enemy with strategically invaluable insights into undersea access routes that could be used to attack some of the millions of Americans who live on or near our coasts."', '"Live,Enemy,Data"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Since the presidency of Ronald Reagan, conservatives have succeeded by adhering to a platform that rests firmly on three legs: smaller government, faith and family, and a strong national defense. These three legs do not merely represent a political coalition; they are three necessary components of a strong and secure America."', '"Faith,Family,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'One of the most important post-9/11 efforts made to counter terrorism and the spread of weapons of mass destruction is President Bush\'s Proliferation Security Initiative (PSI).', '"Important,Security,Terrorism"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"). Dozens of nations have agreed to join in monitoring and, if necessary, intercepting and boarding ships on the high seas in the event they are suspected of engaging in one or both of these threatening activities."', '"Join,High,Monitoring"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'The most desirable aspects of the Law of the Sea Treaty pertain to navigational rights.', '"Law,Sea,Rights"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'The United Nations has long sought the ability to raise revenues in this manner as a means of reducing its reliance on American and other member nations\' dues to sustain the UN\'s operations.', '"Long,American,United Nations"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'The more we are consuming oil that either comes from places that are bent on our destruction or helping those who are... the more we are enabling those who are trying to kill us.', '"Trying,More,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"I don\'t believe there is such a thing as a moderate Islamist party. The challenge with Islamists is that they seek to impose what they call Sharia on everybody, Muslim and non-Muslim alike."', '"Believe,Challenge,Call"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"After all, from the Muslim Brotherhood\'s inception in Egypt in 1928, it has been a revolutionary organization committed to the imposition worldwide of a totalitarian, supremacist Islamic doctrine they call shariah."', '"Organization,Egypt,Brotherhood"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Sharia has become an increasingly significant force in American capitalism, thanks to the embrace by Wall Street and the U.S. government of so-called Sharia-Compliant Finance. Indeed, this country\'s taxpayers now own the largest purveyor of sharia-compliant insurance products in the world: AIG."', '"Finance,Government,World"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'Sharia is the impetus behind multinational diplomatic efforts to accommodate Sharia blasphemy prohibitions on expression that offends Muslims.', '"Behind,Expression,Multinational"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"After America won the Cold War, some believed we had come to the \'end of history,\' and budget-cutters celebrated the so-called \'peace dividend.\' As a result, we ignored the toxic mixture of militant Islam and terror that ultimately led to 9/11."', '"War,History,Peace"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'Most Americans will be horrified that President Obama is compromising our deterrent to chemical and biological attacks on this country. Our allies will also be troubled by his aspiration to eliminate U.S. tactical nuclear weapons in Europe.', '"Country,Will,Europe"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Too many countries that do not play by the free trade rules of the World Trade Organization - including, notably mercantilist China and monopolist Saudi Arabia - have been allowed in, to the detriment of both the WTO and the liberal trading environment it is supposed to sponsor."', '"World,Free,Organization"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', 'It is one of the truisms of politics that a conservative is often enough a former liberal who has been \'mugged by reality.\'', '"Politics,Reality,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"To his lasting credit, President Reagan never wavered. He recognized the strategic importance of staying the course, both in terms of denying Moscow the military hegemony it sought in Western Europe and of restoring the will, cohesiveness, and security of the NATO alliance, so badly frayed during the turbulent 1970s."', '"Security,Will,Credit"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Having worked for him in the nuclear weapons policy business, I can tell you that President Reagan was committed to assuring the effectiveness of our nuclear deterrent."', '"Business,I Can,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"But I really believe it is in America\'s interest as well as that of the free world more generally to stop Iran from getting its hands on nuclear weapons. This regime has threatened to wipe Israel off the map and bring about a world without America, and either of those is a really bad prospect."', '"Believe,World,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe23', '"Ever since taking office, the Obama administration has sought to accommodate Islamist demands that freedom of expression be curbed, lest it offend Muslims and stoke violence. For example, in 2009, the administration co-sponsored a United Nations Human Rights Council resolution along those lines."', '"Freedom,Violence,United Nations"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Architecture should speak of its time and place, but yearn for timelessness."', '"Time,Architecture,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"If I knew where I was going, I wouldn\'t do it. When I can predict or plan it, I don\'t do it."', '"I Can,Predict,Plan"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"For me, every day is a new thing. I approach each project with a new insecurity, almost like the first project I ever did. And I get the sweats. I go in and start working, I\'m not sure where I\'m going. If I knew where I was going I wouldn\'t do it."', '"Work,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'You\'ve got to bumble forward into the unknown.', '"Unknown,Forward,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'The best advice I\'ve received is to be yourself. The best artists do that.', '"Best,Be Yourself,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Liquid architecture. It\'s like jazz - you improvise, you work together, you play off each other, you make something, they make something. And I think it\'s a way of - for me, it\'s a way of trying to understand the city, and what might happen in the city."', '"Work,Architecture,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'Chicago\'s one of the rare places where architecture is more visible.', '"Architecture,Rare,More"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"A lot of people don\'t get it, but I design from the inside out so that the finished product looks inevitable somehow. I think it\'s important to create spaces that people like to be in, that are humanistic."', '"Design,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I would like to make a building as intellectually driven as it is sculptural and as positive as it would be acceptable to hope.', '"Positive,Hope,Building"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I work from the inside out.', '"Work,Inside,Out"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"It\'s not new that architecture can profoundly affect a place, sometimes transform it. Architecture and any art can transform a person, even save someone."', '"Art,Architecture,New"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Architecture has always been a very idealistic profession. It\'s about making the world a better place, and it works over the generations because people go on vacation and they look for it."', '"Architecture,Look,World"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I don\'t think all buildings have to be iconic, but the history of the world has shown us that cultures build iconic buildings for their major public buildings."', '"History,World,Buildings"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Each project, I suffer like I\'m starting over again in life. There\'s a lot of healthy insecurity that fuels this stuff."', '"Life,Insecurity,Project"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I don\'t want to do architecture that\'s dry and dull.', '"Architecture,Want,Dull"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I can\'t just decide myself what\'s being built. Someone decides what they want, then I work for them."', '"Work,Myself,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'Bilbao opened in 1997. It was only ten years later that I was asked to do another museum. A lot of other people got work because of Bilbao.', '"Work,People,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'My buildings are all on budget.', '"Buildings,Budget"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"A well-designed home has to be very comfortable. I can\'t stand the aesthetes, the minimal thing. I can\'t live that way. My home has to be filled with stuff - mostly paintings, sculpture, my fish lamps, cardboard furniture, lots of books."', '"Home,Fish,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Democracy, obviously, is something we don\'t want to give up, but it does create chaos. It means the guy next door can do what he wants, and it creates a collision of thinking. In cities, that means people build whatever they want."', '"Democracy,Thinking,Chaos"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"The fact is I\'m an opportunist. I\'ll take materials around me, materials on my table, and work with them as I\'m searching for an idea that works."', '"Work,Me,Table"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Some people may say my curved panels look like sails. Well, I am a sailor, so I guess I probably do use that metaphor in my work - though not consciously."', '"Work,Look,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I don\'t know how to overcome this perception that I\'m extravagant.', '"Perception,Know,Overcome"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"You have freedom, so you have to make choices - and at the point when I make a choice, the building starts to look like a Frank Gehry building. It\'s a signature."', '"Freedom,Look,Choice"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"My only extravagance in life is my sailboat. I\'m bonkers about that, but other than that, I don\'t spend money on myself."', '"Life,Money,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I used to sketch - that\'s the way I thought out loud. Then they made a book of my sketches, and I got self-conscious, so now I don\'t do it much."', '"Way,Now,Book"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'One of my greatest influences is the Italian artist Gian Lorenzo Bernini.', '"Artist,Greatest,Italian"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"My father was an urchin that lived in Hell\'s Kitchen. He was part of a family of nine. I mean, there were times that were better and worse, but mostly, by the time we got to L.A., they\'d lost whatever they had. And it was a sad time. And both he and I became truck drivers for different companies."', '"Family,Sad,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I approach each project with a new insecurity, almost like the first project I ever did, and I get the sweats, I go in and start working, I\'m not sure where I\'m going."', '"New,Start,Insecurity"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'There is a backlash against me and everyone who has done buildings that have movement and feeling.', '"Me,Done,Buildings"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"When I went to Harvard and studied planning, I found I didn\'t have the skills or the strength to become the kind of public person who could go out and lobby government agencies."', '"Strength,Government,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"The game is if the orchestra can hear each other, they play better. If they play better and there\'s a tangible feeling between the orchestra and the audience, if they feel each other, the audience responds and the orchestra feels it."', '"Game,Better,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I make a model of the site. There are some obvious things: where the entrance should be, where the cars have to go in. You start to get the scale of it. You understand the client\'s needs, and what the client is hoping for and yearning for."', '"Start,Understand,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Architecture is a service business. An architect is given a program, budget, place, and schedule. Sometimes the end product rises to art - or at least people call it that."', '"Business,Art,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'There is stuff I would have liked to have done. But there are no sour grapes.', '"Done,Grapes,Would"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Well, I\'ve always just - I\'ve never really gone out looking for work. I always waited for it to sort of hit me on the head."', '"Work,Me,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I promised a lot of people I\'d slow down when I turned 80.', '"People,Slow,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I never said I was opposed to the LEED program or to green building - I\'m not.', '"Green,Building,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"When I was a kid, my father didn\'t really have much hope for me. He thought I was a dreamer; he didn\'t think I would amount to anything. My mother also."', '"Hope,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"And I realized, when I\'d come in to the meetings with these corrugated metal and chain link stuff, and people would just look at me like I\'d just landed from Mars. But I couldn\'t do anything else. That was my response to the people and the time."', '"Time,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"An architect is given a program, budget, place, and schedule. Sometimes the end product rises to art - or at least people call it that."', '"Art,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Look, architecture has a lot of places to hide behind, a lot of excuses. \'The client made me do this.\' \'The city made me do this.\' \'Oh, the budget.\' I don\'t believe that anymore."', '"Architecture,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"Most of our cities built since the war are bland. They\'re modernist, they\'re cold, and now architects want to go back to that."', '"War,Back,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'This neo-minimalism super cold stuff is weird to me. I need a place where I can come home and take my shoes off.', '"Home,Me,Shoes"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I think my attitudes about the past are very traditional. You can\'t ignore history; you can\'t escape it even if you want to. You might as well know where you come from, and you might as well know that everything has been done in some shape or form."', '"History,Past,Escape"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I don\'t make things with my hands, although I studied woodworking and made furniture."', '"Hands,Furniture,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'There are a lot of questions about whether architecture is art. The people who ask that think pretty tract houses are architecture. But that doesn\'t hold up.', '"Art,Architecture,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'I have always thought that L.A. is a motor city that developed linear downtowns.', '"City,Always,Motor"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"There are people who design buildings that are not technically and financially good, and there are those who do. Two categories - simple."', '"Good,Design,Simple"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'Green issues have been used as a marketing tool. Sometimes these green claims are completely meaningless.', '"Green,Sometimes,Meaningless"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"On certain projects, on big public projects, people definitely are interested in making them greener, but on smaller projects with tight budgets it can be harder."', '"People,Big,Greener"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I was in Peru and visited a building near Lima built by the Incas. It was low in height, with no windows at all, but all the way in the back there was air movement. And I couldn\'t figure out how they\'d done it; it was incredible."', '"Way,Done,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', 'My father probably - he had flashes of creativity - he used to do store windows for fruit stores that he worked in and stuff.', '"Fruit,Father,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I refuse to work unless I get paid, so I don\'t get a lot of work sometimes."', '"Work,Sometimes,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I\'m a leftie, and I\'ve always believed in doing things on a modest scale."', '"Doing,Always,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe24', '"I think people care. If not, why do so many people spend money going on vacations to see architecture? They go to the Parthenon, to Chartres, to the Sydney Opera House. They go to Bilbao... Something compels them, and yet we live surrounded by everything but great architecture."', '"Money,Great,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', 'Gray skies are just clouds passing over.', '"Sports,Clouds,Gray"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', '"Pro football is like nuclear warfare. There are no winners, only survivors."', '"Sports,Football,Winners"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', 'Oh how sweet it is to hear one\'s own convictions from another\'s lips.', '"Sweet,Own,Lips"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', 'I was the law and order.', '"Law,Order,Law And Order"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', '"I had three stages of knowing Wellington Mara. He was my boss for a long time and he was a father figure. And finally, as we got older, he was my friend."', '"Time,Boss,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', '"Before the first year, nobody gave it a chance. Now, 36 years later, everybody knows Monday Night Football."', '"Chance,Football,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe25', 'It is wonderful... Steve and Dan took professional football to a whole different level with the way they played the game. The fact that Steve is going in with Dan is very special.', '"Football,Game,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'ve been doubted my whole life, especially coming out of college with the injuries I had."', '"Life,Injuries,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I could\'ve easily gone the other way, but luckily, I had football and the dream to play in the NFL so I could do something positive with my life."', '"Positive,Life,Football"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'m going to be a Niner, you know, I\'ve been there - that\'s who drafted me, gave me the opportunity to come into this league, to be a professional ball player, and I was there 10 years, man."', '"Opportunity,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'ve been boxing for a while now, and I probably could fight a little bit if I wanted to."', '"Fight,Boxing,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Coming up, I thought Barry Sanders was the best running back ever."', '"Best,Back,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When you think about retiring, you\'re done. You already checked out."', '"Done,Think,About"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'My son going to college is a big milestone.', '"Son,Big,College"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"My neighborhood, Coconut Grove, we always played in the streets. It was corner against corner. We all had football teams. Different neighborhoods."', '"Football,Always,Corner"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"But I look at Anquan Boldin the same. If you watch us, we\'re similar players. We\'re not the fastest, we\'re not the biggest, but we get it done. I think we\'re just football players."', '"Football,Look,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"As long as I stay consistent as my career goes, I\'m good with it."', '"Good,Long,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"To be able to be mentioned with guys like Emmitt, Walter Payton, Barry Sanders, Curtis Martin and my man LaDainian Tomlinson, it\'s a blessing."', '"Man,Blessing,Able"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"My mom, how she raised me, my brothers, my cousins, when I was a kid with one bedroom for 12 people... You think about all that, and God blessed me to get somewhere and do something I love and do something I\'ve done since I was a kid. And blessed me with the talent to do it."', '"Love,God,Mom"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"You think about when I went to Miami. I played as a freshman, I go in and compete to be a starter, I tear my ACL. Come back, I start, I get off to a good couple of games and I get hurt again. You hear everybody saying, \'Oh, he\'s done.\' I get drafted in the third round. People still said I got drafted too high, saying I\'ll only play three years."', '"Good,People,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m not a talker. But I will show in practice the way I work and the way I love the game.', '"Love,Work,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I knew that I wasn\'t the smartest kid in school, but I knew that I had a way to get out if I did the right things in sports."', '"Sports,Way,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'m not the fastest guy, but when it comes to agility, getting in and out of cuts and seeing something and going to get it, I do my best to make sure that\'s on point."', '"Best,Seeing,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Whatever the coach calls, I\'m going to give 110 percent."', '"Whatever,Percent,Coach"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I don\'t care what age I am. If I continue to train and feel good and enjoy the locker room and this organization wants me and I feel I can do it, I\'m going to do it, no matter what my age."', '"Good,Age,Feel Good"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"You can be talented, but having great talent isn\'t enough. You have to work every day or someone will pass you up."', '"Work,Great,Talent"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I love when people tell me what I can\'t do.', '"Love,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I want to make an impact.', '"Impact,Want,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When I\'m done, whenever I feel like I\'m done, I\'m going to come back and retire as a Niner."', '"Feel,Done,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"My first year playing Pop Warner football, my mom had to change my birth certificate because I was too young. I was 5, I think, and you were supposed to be 6."', '"Change,Mom,Football"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"My first time playing running back in a real game, I had eight touchdowns."', '"Time,Game,First Time"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When something you love gets taken away, it hurts you."', '"Love,Something,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"If I feel like I can\'t play ball anymore, I\'ll stop that day. I\'m not a fool. I respect the game too much."', '"Respect,Fool,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"My coaches respect me - the way I come to work, practice and play."', '"Work,Respect,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Before I got injured, football was very easy, I didn\'t have to work out."', '"Work,Football,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"As long as I\'m healthy and feeling good, I will compete with anybody."', '"Good,Long,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I train with young guys in the offseason just to be honest and keep myself sure, to let myself know if I\'m ready or will I be ready."', '"Myself,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I want to show guys that when they get up in age, if you love the game and you go out and work hard, it shouldn\'t matter what age you are."', '"Love,Work,Age"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"People said I would be in the league for two to three years and then I would be done. I have been blessed to keep going, and also have success."', '"Success,Keep Going,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I try my best when I get an opportunity and my number gets called.', '"Best,Opportunity,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I don\'t put nothing past no man who ever played the game of football.', '"Football,Man,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m not scared of any man.', '"Man,Scared,Any"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'Defensive guys don\'t really understand. It\'s totally different for offense. Defensive guys are convinced they know us but they just don\'t understand. Quarterbacks have so much that they have to read and adjust to. They have to look at everybody on the defense. It\'s totally different for the offense.', '"Look,Know,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I know that every team likes a guy who\'s going to try their best and work very hard.', '"Work,Best,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"How I pick running backs, I always go off what situation they\'re in. I look at guys and what they had around them."', '"Look,Situation,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Once I got into the league, I liked to watch LaDainian Tomlinson. He was nice, man. Quick, strong, great eyes, able to catch the ball."', '"Great,Eyes,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'ve been blessed to play 15 years.', '"Blessed,Play,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When you hear coaches say your son is good, sometimes you think they are just saying it because it\'s you."', '"Good,Sometimes,Son"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I take it one game at a time, one year at a time."', '"Time,Game,Year"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When I see a guy on the football field huffing and puffing, I know I got an advantage over him."', '"Football,See,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When you go up against the best of the best, you\'re ready for any type of competition."', '"Best,Competition,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m not selfish.', 'Selfish', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I just always told myself that I can never get big-headed if I become successful.', '"Myself,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m better learning by somebody showing me something. I got to see and then do it. You can\'t be scared to ask for help.', '"Learning,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m very competitive.', '"Competitive,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I don\'t like attention.', '"Attention,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When you come from Miami, you\'re used to winning."', '"Winning,Come,Miami"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I set my goals high.', '"Goals,High,Set"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I don\'t really have a best friend.', '"Best,Friend,Best Friend"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Every time I got opportunities, I did something with it."', '"Time,Something,Did"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'ve been through so much. I mean, after an ACL, you have to learn how to walk again, how to run again, you have to get your head strong again."', '"Walk,Your,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'m from Miami, you know, when you\'re a child, you always want to play in front of your hometown."', '"Hometown,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Some guys go to different teams and as they get older, they just want to ride the coattail of the younger guys. I don\'t want to do that."', '"Ride,Go,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'My kids get to see me every day.', '"Me,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When training camp comes, all the guys in my running back room will see how hard I go every day."', '"Training,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I tried the Xenith helmet later in my career and immediately wished I had done it earlier. It was comfortable, secure, and allowed me to perform without distractions."', '"Me,Done,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When I went to high school, my whole neighborhood, they followed me. They wanted to see me be successful."', '"Me,School,See"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'My first goal was to play in the NFL.', '"First,Play,Goal"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I want to make sure I\'m not the last NFL player to come out of the Grove.', '"Last,Want,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I don\'t want to just be part of a team, I want to help a team, and I don\'t want anyone to say I rode the bench to get a ring."', '"Help,Bench,Just Be"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I have young guys come up to me after games and say they want to train with me and they don\'t know how I do it. It\'s God, it\'s training and it\'s love for the game."', '"Love,God,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I can\'t really grip the ball with my left hand.', '"Ball,Grip,Left"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I just want to go out there and try to get my respect from my teammates and my coaches.', '"Respect,Go,Teammates"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I just think I respect the game and care for the game so much.', '"Respect,Game,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I thought my freshman year at the University of Miami, I was balling, I was looking forward to the NFL."', '"Looking Forward,Looking,University"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I like Coach Harbaugh a lot. No issues.', '"Like,Coach,Issues"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When I\'m tired, I tell myself what the people are saying about me. In that second workout when I\'m saying, \'Man, I don\'t want to do this.\' I remind myself, \'They\'re saying you\'re old. They\'re saying you\'re 33. They\'re saying you can\'t do it this year.\' I play games with myself off that stuff."', '"Myself,Tired,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I try to do two workouts three times a week.', '"Three,Week,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'ve been blessed to make pretty good money over the years.', '"Money,Good,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"If I can go compete with the young guys during training in the offseason, I should be fine during football."', '"Football,Training,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I feel like every year it\'s something with me. I\'ve got to overcome everything every year.', '"Me,Feel,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I watch what I eat a little during the week.', '"Week,Eat,Watch"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I like to work out with the young guys.', '"Work,Young,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Nowadays, kids need promises to play. And I\'m not gonna lie, I almost went to Mississippi. But that\'s the best thing I did, when I changed my mind and went to Miami."', '"Best,Mind,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'You\'ve got to know what helps you be successful during the season.', '"Know,Successful,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"Whatever I feel like I\'m good at, I try my best to do."', '"Best,Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'When you\'re a free agent you want to be wanted.', '"Free,Want,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I train hard.', '"Hard,Train"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"As long as God blesses me in the morning to get up and work hard, I\'m going to take advantage of it."', '"Work,God,Morning"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I was always a hard worker, but when I was younger I didn\'t have to put the extra work in like some of the other guys."', '"Work,Always,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m not a talker unless I really feel I have to say something.', '"Feel,Something,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When it\'s time to play, I\'m going to come play. I\'m going to play the right way. I\'m going to try to help my team in all directions, blocking and catching. If I don\'t have the ball in my hand, I\'m going to protect, block down the field. I\'m going to do whatever it takes to win."', '"Time,Way,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"If you know sports in Dade County, you know me."', '"Sports,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'ve always strived to prove people wrong.', '"People,Always,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I want to be remembered as a guy who played the game of football right.', '"Football,Game,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I\'m not going to be done until the man up above says so. It\'s not me, it\'s Him. As long as I\'m healthy enough to be out there and train and my body feels good, I\'m going to do it."', '"Good,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"I hear all the critics, man. I hear them saying \'He\'s done.\' I hear them saying \'He can\'t.\' I hear all that. That keeps me going."', '"Man,Me,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When you\'re looking from the outside looking in, you don\'t know what\'s in the locker room until you get there."', '"Looking,Know,Room"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"As long as you train and love to compete, you can do whatever you want."', '"Love,Long,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', 'I\'m only a player; I only do what my coach says.', '"Only,Coach,Says"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe26', '"When your name gets mentioned with the great guys that played this game in the past, that\'s very big."', '"Great,Game,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe27', '"I am a man of few words, but many riddles."', '"Man,I Am,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe27', '"The finer the bait, the shorter the wait!"', '"Wait,Bait,Finer"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe27', '"With money, who needs friends?"', '"Money,Needs,Friends"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'Israel changed my life. It is one of the most amazing countries that I have ever been to.', '"Life,Amazing,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"My favorite movie is \'The Outlaw Josey Wales\' with Clint Eastwood, a guy who gets his family killed by the bad guys then goes on a journey of revenge, eventually discovering himself - very existential."', '"Family,Journey,Revenge"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"Coming from immigrant Italian people, the one thing you do is work hard."', '"Work,People,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"When you have Liam Neeson in a film, no matter how good everyone else is, it\'s a Liam Neeson film. And if there\'s wolves, and you\'re running, it\'s about Liam Neeson running from wolves."', '"Good,Matter,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'There\'s nobody in the arts in my family. It was kind of embarrassing to even say that I wanted to be an actor.', '"Family,Nobody,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"A tough guy, to me, stands for something, and he\'s not afraid to get a beating."', '"Me,Tough,Tough Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I\'m a believer in getting punched in the face. I know it sounds cliched, but to me, fighting is a metaphor for life."', '"Life,Face,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I can see parts of my father in \'Kingdom\' when I rage like that. I can see my father\'s frustrations in his life.', '"Life,Father,See"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"What people don\'t know is that I\'m a blackbelt in jujitsu, which I\'ve been for 20 years, and I\'ve been boxing since I\'ve been 15 years old - those are things that come natural to me."', '"Me,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'Anthony Bourdain is a legend and an inspiration for me.', '"Me,Legend,Inspiration"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"When I graduated college, I decided that I was going to try to be an actor, but it was my dirty secret."', '"Dirty,Secret,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I was a wrestler. I played football, lacrosse. After high school, I got into jujitsu. I boxed my whole adult life."', '"Life,Football,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"A film that I love is \'Deliverance\' from back in the day. You start out with these archetypal characters - the hero, the bookworm, the pacifist - and by the end, it\'s all turned upside down. I love that."', '"Love,Love Is,Hero"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"You\'ve got to go out there and do your things. Whatever comes your way, you jump on it, and like anything, that\'s how you get your experience."', '"Experience,Way,Jump"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I did \'The Grey,\' and it was very intense and emotional because we\'re in the wilderness, and it was always 30 degrees. You kind of lose your sense of reality in the fact that you\'re filming a movie."', '"Reality,Lose,Grey"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I\'m not really enamored by movie stars.', '"Stars,Really,Movie"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'What I look for in a role is the physical. But what\'s the journey emotionally? Can I take this person who is this archetypal tough guy and find the beauty?', '"Beauty,Journey,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I grew up with no money. No money. I always struggled and had the sense that there was this other class of people who went to college - this was when I was younger.', '"Money,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"Listen, \'The Purge\' actually exists in some form or another in many places around the world when you think about it."', '"World,Places,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"You get spoiled on \'Captain America,\' where your trailer\'s two blocks long and it\'s got three bedrooms."', '"Long,America,Captain"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"The soap opera was so long ago - the thing about soap operas, and there\'s something to be said for doing it, but you do a script a day. I don\'t want to say it\'s a training ground; it really isn\'t, but what it does teach you is discipline."', '"Discipline,Long,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I\'m a physical person - I like to get hit.', '"Person,Like,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"There was nobody telling me, \'You should be an artist,\' or, \'You should be an actor.\'"', '"Me,Nobody,Artist"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"A lot of times, especially with TV, I would get these scripts, and I\'m like, \'Oh, they want me to be the good-looking guy who\'s a little bit of a rascal.\' It\'s just boring."', '"Me,Boring,Good-Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'Being an actor can be a lonely life.', '"Life,Actor,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I have always been restless. I have always been a seeker. It is one of the reasons that I train as hard as I do and I have studied as many disciplines as I have. I need to be challenged.', '"Always,Hard,Train"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I wrestled when I was a kid. That started me off with the discipline, because making weight was my responsibility. It is a team sport, but it is also a solo sport."', '"Discipline,Me,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"My friend Liam Neeson has managed to carve out a great place in the industry for himself and is still doing action movies at 64 years old. He\'s my hero. I use him as a template. My middle kid, Liam, is named after him. He\'s one of the coolest guys in Hollywood."', '"Great,Movies,Hero"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"The things that make me saddest - when I got into my head - if anything were to happen to me, and my wife were to have to go to my kids and say \'Daddy\'s gone.\' Worst thing I could imagine."', '"Wife,Me,Worst"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '\'The Outlaw Josey Wales\' is one of my top three movies.', '"Movies,Three,Top"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I love \'The Dirty Dozen.\'', '"Love,Dirty,I Love"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I love Charles Bronson. He didn\'t have a lot of range, and he wasn\'t a great actor, but you couldn\'t take your eyes off him."', '"Love,Great,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I have a good work ethic.', '"Work,Good,Good Work"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"My parents got married when they were 16, and they never had any money."', '"Money,Parents,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I\'m not talented.', 'Talented', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I think it just seems like something that somebody else does, like they raise actors somewhere in Ohio, and once in a while, people go and pick their actors and move to Hollywood. It seemed like such a distant idea. But then, as I started growing up, I\'m like, \'Oh, this is an occupation.\'"', '"People,Go,Somewhere"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"When directors like Joe Russo, who understand story from a very global perspective, start working more and more with Chinese filmmakers, you\'ll start seeing Chinese films that connect with audiences all over Asia, Europe, and South America - maybe even North America."', '"Perspective,America,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', '"I find in L.A. that you ask people how they\'re doing, and the immediate answer is, \'Oh, I\'m very busy,\' as if busy is the goal."', '"Busy,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe28', 'I don\'t look like Hollywood Guy. I\'m a regular guy.', '"Look,Hollywood,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe29', 'As long as I am mayor of this city the great industries are secure.', '"Great,Long,City"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe29', '"You hear about constitutional rights, free speech and the free press. Every time I hear these words I say to myself, \'That man is a Red, that man is a Communist!\' You never hear a real American talk like that."', '"Time,Myself,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', '"There is a destiny that shapes our ends rough, hew them as we will."', '"Destiny,Will,Rough"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', 'Strong people are made by opposition like kites that go up against the wind.', '"Wind,People,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', '"All the faults of the age come from Christianity and journalism. Christianity, of course, but why journalism?"', '"Age,Journalism,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', '"The Christian churches were offered two things: the spirit of Jesus and the idiotic morality of Paul, and they rejected the higher inspiration... Following Paul, we have turned the goodness of love into a fiend and degraded the crowning impulse of our being into a capital sin."', '"Love,Spirit,Sin"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', 'Memoirs are a well-known form of fiction.', '"Fiction,Form,Memoirs"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', 'Sex is the gateway to life.', '"Life,Sex,Gateway"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2a', '"I am, really, a great writer; my only difficulty is in finding great readers."', '"Great,I Am,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"I must not fear. Fear is the mind-killer. Fear is the little-death that brings total obliteration. I will face my fear. I will permit it to pass over me and through me. And when it has gone past, I will turn the inner eye to see its path. Where the fear has gone, there will be nothing. Only I will remain."', '"Fear,Path,Face"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"Without change, something sleeps inside us, and seldom awakens. The sleeper must awaken."', '"Change,Inside,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"He who can destroy a thing, can control a thing."', '"Control,Destroy,He"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"Think you of the fact that a deaf person cannot hear. Then, what deafness may we not all possess? What senses do we lack that we cannot see and cannot hear another world all around us?"', '"World,See,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Seek freedom and become captive of your desires. Seek discipline and find your liberty.', '"Freedom,Discipline,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'The beginning of knowledge is the discovery of something we do not understand.', '"Knowledge,Beginning,Discovery"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"Any road followed precisely to its end leads precisely nowhere. Climb the mountain just a little bit to test it\'s a mountain. From the top of the mountain, you cannot see the mountain."', '"Road,See,End"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"Enemies make you stronger, allies make you weaker."', '"Enemies,Stronger,Allies"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"Wealth is a tool of freedom, but the pursuit of wealth is the way to slavery."', '"Freedom,Wealth,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Respect for the truth comes close to being the basis for all morality.', '"Respect,Truth,Morality"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'How often it is that the angry man rages denial of what his inner self is telling him.', '"Anger,Angry,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Kindness is the beginning of cruelty.', '"Kindness,Beginning,Cruelty"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'There is no escape - we pay for the violence of our ancestors.', '"Escape,Ancestors,Violence"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"When law and duty are one, united by religion, you never become fully conscious, fully aware of yourself. You are always a little less than an individual."', '"Religion,Yourself,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'What do you despise? By this are you truly known.', '"Truly,Known,Despise"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Truth suffers from too much analysis.', '"Truth,Too Much,Analysis"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Something cannot emerge from nothing.', '"Nothing,Cannot,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'The proximity of a desirable thing tempts one to overindulgence. On that path lies danger.', '"Path,Danger,Lies"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"To suspect your own mortality is to know the beginning of terror, to learn irrefutably that you are mortal is to know the end of terror."', '"Beginning,End,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'To attempt seeing Truth without knowing Falsehood. It is the attempt to see the Light without knowing the Darkness. It cannot be.', '"Truth,Light,Darkness"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"If you think of yourselves as helpless and ineffectual, it is certain that you will create a despotic government to be your master. The wise despot, therefore, maintains among his subjects a popular sense that they are helpless and ineffectual."', '"Government,Wise,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"The difference between sentiment and being sentimental is the following: Sentiment is when a driver swerves out of the way to avoid hitting a rabbit on the road. Being sentimental is when the same driver, when swerving away from the rabbit, hits a pedestrian."', '"Way,Road,Avoid"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', '"It is a wise man that does know the contented man is never poor, whilst the discontented man is never rich."', '"Wise,Man,Wise Man"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'Religion often partakes of the myth of progress that shields us from the terrors of an uncertain future.', '"Future,Religion,Progress"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'The stakes in conflict do not change. Battle determines who will control the wealth or its equivalent.', '"Change,Battle,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'The people I distrust most are those who want to improve our lives but have only one course of action.', '"Action,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2b', 'One of the best things to come out of the home computer revolution could be the general and widespread understanding of how severely limited logic really is.', '"Best,Home,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2c', 'There is nothing that can help you understand your beliefs more than trying to explain them to an inquisitor.', '"Nothing,Help,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2c', '"There is one advantage to having nothing, it never needs repair."', '"Nothing,Never,Repair"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"If you don\'t listen, you\'re never gonna learn."', '"Never,Gonna,Listen"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"The relationship between \'My Chemical Romance\' and Michael Pedicone is over. He was caught red-handed stealing from the band and confessed to police after our show last night in Auburn, Washington. We are heartbroken and sick to our stomachs over this entire situation."', '"Relationship,Night,Police"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"The best music happens when you have a personal connection to it. That same philosophy can extend to the instrument you hold in your hands: if a guitar means something special, you\'re bound to do great things with it."', '"Best,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'About six years ago my family was affected by multiple sclerosis.', '"Family,Six,About"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"My first show was when I was a high school freshman, but it was at the junior class dance. My older friend and bandmate booked it."', '"Dance,School,Friend"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I also remember the second band I was in ever. We were called Hybrid. We got a show at this local street fair, and we were playing on the back of a flatbed truck. There was an ad in the paper, and it said that \'Hybird\' is playing. I was so mad."', '"Remember,Street,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'A guitar solo in the same part of every tune - that\'s been done so much. I think solos shine more when you have them in specific and unexpected places.', '"Guitar,Unexpected,Shine"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"MS is terrible for anybody, and all of the stories are important."', '"Important,Terrible,Stories"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"My dad was very influential with the music he exposed me to. He was really into blues and folk, so he\'d play me guys like Muddy Waters and T-Bone Walker and Richie Havens - a lot of very emotional players."', '"Music,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'I have no want or desire to solo. I\'d rather create melodies and accompanying parts.', '"Create,Desire,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"We\'ve always wanted to do it, something you could dance to, and deep down we always thought we could bring something to the table if we could do it, but the live shows always made us pull back and be a rock band."', '"Dance,Live,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"Publishing the lyric books, poetry or comics of other musicians I know. That\'s the thing I really want to break into!"', '"Poetry,Know,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I think my least favourite thing to listen to is perfect songs, perfect performances. They don\'t feel human to me, and in that respect ,they lose any kind of sincerity. I don\'t know why. It\'s just my ears."', '"Respect,Me,Lose"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I grew up in that band. Some people go to college and get a Master\'s. I went to My Chem academy, and I feel like I graduated with honors."', '"Feel,People,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I\'m kind of a feel player. I\'ll stretch out before a show a bit and do some playing, but that\'s about it. I\'m not one of these 10-hour-a-day playing guys."', '"Feel,Show,About"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"These days, all we hear about is that the industry is in trouble. Everybody is so scared, but our mission statement is having no fear."', '"Fear,Mission,No Fear"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'People don\'t always realize that a record is forever. It\'ll always be there under your name. You\'ve got to be certain that it\'s right.', '"People,Name,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"Anytime you put yourself in a creative box, it\'s going to stifle you; it\'s not conducive to the writing or recording process."', '"Yourself,Process,Recording"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"When you break it all down, my punk rock is my dad\'s blues. It\'s music from the underground, and it\'s real, and it\'s written for the downtrodden in uncertain times."', '"Music,Dad,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I love players like Thurston Moore. I mean, you can put notes down on a sheet of paper, and if you practice and get your chops up, you can play like an Eddie Van Halen or a Steve Vai. But nobody can do what Thurston Moore does; he\'s his own guy. He talks through his instrument in a language that\'s all his own."', '"Love,Practice,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'I always wanted to be in bands.', '"Always,Wanted,Bands"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"My father gave me one of those small, box-sized travel players when I was a kid and just a handful of records that he had. \'Zeppelin IV\' was one. \'The Beatles at the Hollywood Bowl,\' which is just about the worst record ever - you can\'t hear anything, just screaming in the background. I think there was maybe, like, an Animals record."', '"Travel,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'I have \'Purple Rain\' on purple vinyl.', '"Rain,Purple,Vinyl"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I think the days of just filling the time and putting a disc out is over, and I\'m glad, because those are some of my least favourite records."', '"Time,Because,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"I miss Jersey so much; I\'m really connected to it. I love the big malls, the diners."', '"Love,Big,Connected"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', '"With our first record, we wrote concept songs but not a concept record."', '"First,Concept,Our"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2d', 'I\'m a fan of records you get and you listen to them from beginning to finish - records where everything is there for a purpose. There was never any filler on those records - it was all well planned out.', '"Purpose,Beginning,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2e', 'We sometime didn\'t get enough to buy oats for our horses. Most banks had very little money in them.', '"Money,Enough,Buy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2e', 'I have been hunted for twenty-one years. I have literally lived in the saddle. I have never known a day of perfect peace.', '"Peace,Perfect,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2e', '"When I slept it was literally in the midst of an arsenal. If I heard dogs bark more fiercely than usual, or the feet of horses in a greater volume of sound than usual, I stood to arms."', '"Feet,Sound,More"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2e', 'I was tired of an outlaw\'s life.', '"Life,Tired,Outlaw"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2e', '"It was one long, anxious, inexorable, eternal vigil."', '"Long,Eternal,Anxious"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2f', 'Our extended family is an integral part of our daily lives and Connie and I welcome you with open arms.', '"Family,Daily,Welcome"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe2f', '"We daily share emotions, our personal and shared needs and hope."', '"Hope,Daily,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe30', 'I think there are a number of bishops - and I put Cardinal Mahony in that category - who listen too much to his lawyer and not enough to his heart.', '"Heart,Lawyer,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe30', '"With or without a Social Security fix, Americans don\'t have enough assets to retire on. There has to be a much larger debate."', '"Debate,Security,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', 'In the long run all producers are forced to use the most efficient methods or give place to others who do.', '"Long,Place,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', '"We have to adapt and overcome, that\'s all we can do."', '"Overcome,Adapt"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', 'All science is static in the sense that it describes the unchanging aspects of things.', '"Science,Things,Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', 'There is no sense in making statements that will not continue to be true after they are made.', '"No Sense,True,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', '"Goods move in response to price differences from points of low to points of higher price, the movement tending to obliterate the price difference and come to rest."', '"Rest,Differences,Difference"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', '"It is true practically if not altogether without exception that the changes studied by any science tend to equilibrate or neutralize the forces which bring them about, and finally to come to rest."', '"Science,Rest,True"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe31', '"The possibility of saying anything about a thing rests on the assumption that it preserves its identity, or continues to be the same thing in the respect described, that it will behave in future situations as it has in past."', '"Respect,Future,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', 'Patriotism was a living fire of unquestioned belief and purpose.', '"Patriotism,Memorial Day,Fire"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', 'God did not intend the human family to be wafted to heaven on flowery beds of ease.', '"Family,God,Heaven"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', '"No matter what happens, the U.S. Navy is not going to be caught napping."', '"Matter,Happens,Caught"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', 'I believe with all my heart that civilization has produced nothing finer than a man or woman who thinks and practices true tolerance.', '"Heart,Man,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', '"Some one has said that most of us don\'t think, we just occasionally rearrange our prejudices."', '"Us,Think,Said"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe32', '"I suspect that even today, with all the progress we have made in liberal thought, the quality of true tolerance is as rare as the quality of mercy."', '"Today,Progress,Quality"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"To be honest, I was Mum\'s boy. Always was, always will be."', '"Will,Always,Boy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"If I lose the ball, I lose it trying to do the right thing. That\'s the way it is."', '"Lose,Do The Right Thing,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'Scoring goals is the best feeling you can have. I always look up at the stand for my family straight afterwards; it means everything to me that they travel to every game.', '"Best,Family,Travel"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'Goals never come easy. No one gives you goals.', '"Goals,Never,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I always dedicate my goals to my mum. I lost her a couple of years ago. She was my biggest supporter and is always with me.', '"Me,Goals,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I can\'t stress the importance of working hard enough, work on all aspects of your game. If you does that and you have the ability, you\'ll come through."', '"Work,Game,Stress"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'You remember the finals you lose as much as the ones you win.', '"Lose,Remember,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"When I was at school, I wanted to be a lawyer."', '"Lawyer,School,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Reading and writing is so important, and it\'s something I am really keen to promote. It\'s something that can be a bit lost these days with so much else going on."', '"I Am,Lost,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'Everyone\'s got unfinished business with Barcelona. They\'re the greatest team in the world.', '"Business,World,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"For present buying, I go to Harrods because there are great personal shoppers, who point me in the right direction."', '"Great,Me,Direction"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I didn\'t want to be the rebel who was bottom of the class, so I worked hard. They wanted me to stay on for A-Levels, but football came calling - that was my real love."', '"Love,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I like to go to America. That\'s where I go for most of my holidays.', '"America,Go,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"If I ever have a son, I would call him Frankie, and it\'s a family name - it\'s my dad and my dad\'s dad, so you know, it sticks. I won\'t forget it."', '"Family,Dad,Son"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I have made lots of mistakes on and off the pitch, and you can only learn from them. If I can get that across, then hopefully I am doing something right."', '"I Am,Mistakes,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I was always pretty good at school, but a lot of it was memorising, maybe cheating off your mates, stuff that gets you through."', '"Good,Cheating,School"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I think as far as kids go, you just have to work hard. Work on your skills, keep focused."', '"Work,Hard Work,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I\'m like everyone else: I want to play every game, but it\'s not possible."', '"Game,Possible,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"People can talk about my age for as long as they like. There is nothing better in football than proving people wrong, and I\'ll try to do that for as long as I can."', '"Age,Football,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Footballers do get a hard time, and there is a lot of generalization going on. When you get to meet players and know them as lads, it\'s always a bit different."', '"Time,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I\'m happy here, and why change when you love the club and the club\'s in a really good position right now."', '"Love,Change,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Nobody expects a footballer to have any kind of an IQ, which is a bit of an unfair stereotype."', '"Nobody,Footballer,Unfair"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I admit I was somewhat concerned when we started to sign so many players - naturally you are going to worry about whether you can retain your place in the side.', '"Worry,Place,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I think it was in Moscow last year and I got changed for training the day before we played Moscow, but the fact is they actually wanted to do John\'s, me and John were next to each other and they did mine by mistake. John had done them I think. So yeah it is true."', '"Me,Training,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"My dad shaped the footballing side of me, and Mum shaped me as a person. I\'ve always been very close to her - we\'ve only ever had one argument, and that was over something stupid when I was 13."', '"Dad,Stupid,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Even with the quality of players that we have, they\'re an extremely hard side to break down and once they get on top of you, you find it difficult to stem the flow of attacks."', '"Quality,Difficult,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I\'m really happy here. I think anyone who knows me well, and the fans too I hope, they know that I love the area, and the bond that I\'ve had with the fans has been fantastic."', '"Love,Hope,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I don\'t think Wayne Rooney would be affected if you booed him, that\'s just how he is, but others go under. They really suffer with it. I think I\'m somewhere in the middle... now. I\'ve become tougher as I\'ve got older."', '"Go,Somewhere,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I have never seen a player as driven and determined as me, quietly determined; that\'s why I always want to do the best."', '"Best,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"When you see young players coming into the squad and pushing you, no matter what age you are, you have to react. You have to worry about yourself and perform as well as you can. If you end up looking around at others, wondering who\'s performing better, you take your eye off the ball."', '"Age,Yourself,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I come from a football family which has really helped.', '"Family,Football,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I\'m not silly. I understand that, with age and at different parts of your career, you have different challenges."', '"Age,Challenges,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I am certainly not the most talented player in the world; there\'s many a more talented player than me.', '"Me,World,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I\'m not the kind of player to see out my time and sit with my bum on the bench too much. I want to be involved. That\'s my character.', '"Time,Character,See"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I think I work harder on the pitch, I cover more ground and my passing is more accurate."', '"Work,Ground,More"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"There\'s that talent thing where I can score goals, and there\'s also that want and ambition to keep doing it and doing it and doing it. I\'ve seen a lot of players do it for a year and then they rest on their laurels, but I\'ve been very driven throughout my career. Without being the most talented, I think I\'ve tried to make the most of it."', '"Goals,Talent,Rest"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I don\'t want to be a passenger sitting on the bench not doing much, even in my older years."', '"Doing,Sitting,Bench"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Training\'s completely different now. It used to be a lot of running and work without the ball. Now it\'s all with the ball, which any player loves."', '"Work,Training,Ball"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I\'m a very private person, and you have a lot of people looking into your personal life, away from football. That\'s the one thing that I don\'t like, but I always remember how lucky we are that we\'re playing football."', '"Life,Football,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Reading with my children is incredibly important to me and a wonderful way to spend time together as a family, exploring magical worlds through books and stories."', '"Family,Time,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'When you take a lot of stick you want to ram it down people\'s throats.', '"People,Down,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"A lot of things happened when I left there, and to be fair they treated me really bad, and now I have to play against them so I don\'t have any feelings for them at all."', '"Me,Bad,Feelings"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I am a man who likes to play consistently; I always play better when I\'m on a run of games.', '"Man,I Am,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I don\'t know if we\'d have been as dominant as we were last season. The new things, the new ideas the manager brought in everyone took them on board so well. He is special."', '"New,Ideas,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I think about all my successes and failures, and sometimes the failures stick in your head as much as the wins. But you do move on."', '"Sometimes,Your,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"I have a lot of good football talk with cabbies, but when you want to get somewhere in a hurry, it can be distracting. I always know they\'re going to want to talk football if \'Talksport\' is on the radio."', '"Good,Football,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I\'ve enjoyed every minute of travelling and playing for my country. What an honour that is.', '"Country,Minute,Enjoyed"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"If players are performing for you, their age shouldn\'t really matter, especially because the older players can bring their experience to the table."', '"Experience,Age,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Barcelona are my favourite team in Spain, let\'s put it that way."', '"Way,Team,Barcelona"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I loved reading Roald Dahl when I was young but I had forgotten a lot about the books. I read the \'BFG\' on the iPad the other day and it was so interesting to see his descriptions of clothes and places.', '"Day,See,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"In international football, you need pace and you need your players up top to create things out of nothing and run at people."', '"Football,People,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Of course, there will be few people who are sympathetic but you don\'t become a great team overnight, no matter how much money you have at your disposal."', '"Money,Great,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'I fancy our chances at the European Championships.', '"Fancy,Championships,Chances"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', '"Every season will have its dips and hard moments, and the challenge then is to make sure you don\'t get too down in those moments and make sure you come back fighting."', '"Fighting,Will,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'Being faster would probably make me better at football.', '"Football,Me,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'Of course it is going to be difficult for any player to get in the Chelsea side no matter who they are.', '"Difficult,Matter,Side"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe33', 'The advantage does lie with us because we\'re at home and if we can\'t motivate ourselves for this match then we can\'t motivate ourselves for any match. I think the crowd will be up for it as well.', '"Home,Lie,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe34', '"If you want to see the sunshine, you have to weather the storm."', '"Weather,Storm,Sunshine"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe34', 'My fingers are not as fast as my brain - which isn\'t that much to type home about anyway.', '"Home,Brain,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I grew up in a household where everybody lived at the top of his lungs.', '"Home,Lungs,Top"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'Intelligence is enormously sexy.', '"Intelligence,Sexy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'One of the safest places to be in the world is the stage.', '"World,Stage,Places"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I have a list a mile long of faults that sometimes bring me to my knees in self-hatred.', '"Me,Long,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"The best kind of kinky sex is to have kinky sex with your wife or husband, the person you love."', '"Love,Best,Sex"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"I just feel that no matter what comes in a career - and mine has been all over the map - you must stay at the table, pick up the cards you\'re dealt and play them."', '"Feel,Cards,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'The last few years have been pretty hectic.', '"Hectic,Last,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'And the test for any actor is whether you stay at the table or go away.', '"Go,Table,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I now want to be playing parts more interesting to me and more exciting to me.', '"Me,More,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"I have always felt the basis of everything in life is sexual, and I will maintain that to my dying day."', '"Life,Day,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"There are no taboos in bed, and there shouldn\'t be any taboos in bed."', '"Bed,Any,Taboos"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"You start acting in spite of your neuroses, not because of them."', '"Start,Acting,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"There\'s a great deal of attention paid and books written about this change of life in a woman, and really very little written about a man\'s change of life."', '"Life,Change,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"It\'s interesting to fantasize having a man sink his teeth into your neck for sustenance, knowing that it isn\'t going to be terribly painful but rather very exciting."', '"Man,Teeth,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'Physical qualities don\'t really matter much.', '"Matter,Qualities,Physical"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"Revelations come when you\'re in the thick of it, pitting yourself up against something larger than yourself."', '"Yourself,Against,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'My body of work means nothing to me.', '"Work,Me,Body"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"Each of us needs something - food, liquor, pot, whatever - to help us survive. Dracula needs blood."', '"Food,Help,Survive"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'Vampires are sexy to a woman perhaps because the fantasy is similar to that of the man on the white horse sweeping her off to paradise.', '"Sexy,Man,Paradise"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I\'d always felt a man should marry later in life.', '"Life,Man,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'But I firmly believe that you can\'t be emotionally free until you are emotionally committed.', '"Believe,Free,Until"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I\'m a firm believer in absolute honesty.', '"Honesty,Believer,Firm Believer"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I always signed autographs when I could and always stayed and chatted with them when I could.', '"Always,Them,Could"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"However, I don\'t by any means suggest that I\'m always playing myself."', '"Myself,Always,Playing"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"As a matter of fact, I rarely ever play myself."', '"Myself,Matter,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"Then, for a hot three or four weeks I wanted to be a concert pianist."', '"Hot,Three,Four"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"But when I was seven or eight, I did my first little piece of acting."', '"Acting,First,Seven"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"What helped me most were my failures and slumps - when I couldn\'t get work, people weren\'t interested in me or had written me off."', '"Work,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'The only thing you have then to believe in is your craft.', '"Believe,Craft,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"But in order to be the thing you want to be, you have to work like a dog at the thing you love."', '"Love,Work,Dog"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"If you\'re lucky as you get older, you respect the craft and it becomes a skill."', '"Respect,Skill,Craft"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'There is no right in acting.', '"Acting,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I watch actors destroy themselves by trying to get it right.', '"Trying,Right,Destroy"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', '"It\'s a living, breathing thing, acting."', '"Acting,Living,Breathing"', '2023-05-29 12:00:00', '2023-05-29 12:00:00'),
	('397849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'Absolutely. I can produce. I can write. I can direct.', '"I Can,Direct,Absolutely"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'But I think one of the reasons I tend to stay in the water most of the time is I distrust the comfort.', '"Time,Water,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'We do most of what we do out of our sexual energy and our sexual needs.', '"Energy,Needs,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe35', 'I\'m hardly a saint.', '"Saint,Hardly"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
