	('397854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', '"One thing I have learned in my time in politics is that if one of the parties is shameless, the other party cannot afford to be spineless."', '"Politics,Time,I Have Learned"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', 'Should those whose actions lead to the death or injury of a child get a free pass?', '"Death,Free,Child"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', '"I say I don\'t need a tax cut. It will not do me any more good. I can\'t buy more, I can\'t eat more, I can\'t do more, and I want it distributed among the ordinary people who work every day."', '"Work,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', '"Anybody who has ever been in business, anybody who has ever paid bills, anybody who has ever lived in a serious adult life knows that indebtedness is a killer."', '"Life,Business,Serious"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', 'The President should spend his time going after the terrorists rather than sharing sensitive counter terrorism information with countries that sponsor terrorism.', '"Time,Information,Terrorism"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe36', '"I had hoped to hear the President tonight tell the Congress and the American people exactly how he plans to tackle some of the important issues facing this country, unfortunately I did not."', '"People,Country,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
