	('397872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'No house should ever be on a hill or on anything. It should be of the hill. Belonging to it. Hill and house should live together each the happier for the other.', '"Together,Hill,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
