	('397905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"The physician can bury his mistakes, but the architect can only advise his client to plant vines - so they should go as far as possible from home to build their first buildings."', '"Home,Plant,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"\'Think simple\' as my old master used to say - meaning reduce the whole of its parts into the simplest terms, getting back to first principles."', '"Simple,Back,Principles"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'The architect should strive continually to simplify; the ensemble of the rooms should then be carefully considered that comfort and utility may go hand in hand with beauty.', '"Beauty,Comfort,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Organic buildings are the strength and lightness of the spiders\' spinning, buildings qualified by light, bred by native character to environment, married to the ground."', '"Strength,Character,Light"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"An architect\'s most useful tools are an eraser at the drafting board, and a wrecking bar at the site."', '"Tools,Useful,Bar"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'Get the habit of analysis - analysis will in time enable synthesis to become your habit of mind.', '"Time,Mind,Habit"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"A great architect is not made by way of a brain nearly so much as he is made by way of a cultivated, enriched heart."', '"Great,Heart,Brain"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Youth is a quality, not a matter of circumstances."', '"Youth,Quality,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Harvard takes perfectly good plums as students, and turns them into prunes."', '"Good,Harvard,Students"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'Mechanization best serves mediocrity.', '"Best,Technology,Mediocrity"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"A free America... means just this: individual freedom for all, rich or poor, or else this system of government we call democracy is only an expedient to enslave man to the machine and make him like it."', '"Politics,Freedom,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"God is the great mysterious motivator of what we call nature, and it has often been said by philosophers, that nature is the will of God. And I prefer to say that nature is the only body of God that we shall ever see."', '"Nature,God,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Life always rides in strength to victory, not through internationalism... but only through the direct responsibility of the individual."', '"Life,Strength,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Respect the masterpiece. It is true reverence to man. There is no quality so great, none so much needed now."', '"Respect,Great,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'New York City is a great monument to the power of money and greed... a race for rent.', '"Money,Power,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Why, I just shake the buildings out of my sleeves."', '"Why,Buildings,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"I believe totally in a Capitalist System, I only wish that someone would try it."', '"Believe,Wish,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'To look at the cross-section of any plan of a big city is to look at something like the section of a fibrous tumor.', '"Look,City,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'Noble life demands a noble architecture for noble uses of noble men. Lack of culture means what it has always meant: ignoble civilization and therefore imminent downfall.', '"Life,Men,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'Bureaucrats: they are dead at 30 and buried at 60. They are like custard pies; you can\'t nail them to a wall.', '"Dead,Like,Custard"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"A man is a fool if he drinks before he reaches the age of 50, and a fool if he doesn\'t afterward."', '"Age,Man,Fool"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'The heart is the chief feature of a functioning mind.', '"Heart,Mind,Feature"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"I have been black and blue in some spot, somewhere, almost all my life from too intimate contacts with my own furniture."', '"Life,Black,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Maybe we can show government how to operate better as a result of better architecture. Eventually, I think Chicago will be the most beautiful great city left in the world."', '"Great,Government,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'I feel coming on a strange disease - humility.', '"Humility,Feel,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', 'The Lincoln Memorial is related to the toga and the civilization that wore it.', '"Civilization,Related,Memorial"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe39', '"Well, now that he\'s finished one building, he\'ll go write four books about it."', '"Building,Go,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"Life has its ups and downs, but you can only look forward."', '"Life,Ups And Downs,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"The human being is very resourceful. When you fight for survival, you don\'t think much; you just do. If you think too much, you sink."', '"Fight,Survival,Too Much"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'The loss of my father was the most traumatic event in my life - I can\'t forget the pain.', '"Life,Pain,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"The loss of my father marked my life. I\'m 88 years old and I\'m still mourning him because it\'s such a drama for me. It was just after my bar mitzvah and it was so tragic. The effect on me, I carry it all my life."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"Money is misunderstood. The fact is if you want to be successful - the money will follow you. If you are a doctor, something else will follow you. If you are successful, there is an accompaniment. If your goal is just to make money, you won\'t succeed. Money is a commodity to use, not to be dictated by."', '"Money,Doctor,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'As a teenager I became a boat person - a refugee - as I made my way to Palestine.', '"Boat,Way,Palestine"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I have... been disturbed by the negative tone of the debate over immigration... there is a rising crescendo of opinion from columnists and politicians saying we should reduce our immigration intake.', '"Negative,Debate,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"So you\'ve got to test the envelope, find out what are your abilities and if you falter, pick yourself up and test it again. Otherwise, what is it all about, you know?"', '"Yourself,Know,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I knew that Britain and the United States were beacons of freedom and democracy at a time when my life - and Western civilisation itself - was at grave risk.', '"Life,Freedom,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"When I was a lone soldier I didn\'t have a penny with me. Everybody was eating hummus with tehina and ate falafel, and I couldn\'t buy it. I was a little hungry, but I managed."', '"Me,Eating,Soldier"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"What is it to enjoy life? Sit at the beach? No. What it is is that you have to do something, you have be productive, make a contribution to the society, to the family, to yourself."', '"Life,Family,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'As a boy I stood at the doorway of our hiding place in Budapest and watched Russian troops fight house by house to liberate the city and therefore rescue us from certain death.', '"Death,Fight,City"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"From morning when I wake up until I go to sleep, I am working. I go to bed and I want to switch off, but the brain doesn\'t switch off."', '"Morning,Brain,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"As a child I learned what it meant to be persecuted. But, even then, at the worst of times, I knew there was good in the world."', '"Good,World,Worst"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"I don\'t remember all my successes, but I do remember failures."', '"Remember,Failures,Successes"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I am 84 years old and have not retired because I feel I have something to contribute.', '"I Am,Feel,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"So many times I wanted to go to Auschwitz, but I couldn\'t take up the courage to go there."', '"Courage,Go,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"I work all the time; whatever I do, I do it, and I don\'t necessarily look at it as work. You could say the Auschwitz project was work, or the Lowy Institute is work, or Westfield is work, or the football is work. It is life."', '"Life,Work,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"I don\'t think of myself as a hard man, but other people may think otherwise. You know you have obligations to do the best you can for people, for your job, for your shareholders... it all has to be balanced between the hardness and the softness."', '"Best,Myself,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'The word \'no\' is not for me. I don\'t hear it. You always have to try again and again.', '"Me,Always,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"All I was looking for is to be successful. I had the opportunity with Australia, with what it provided for me economically."', '"Opportunity,Me,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"I wanted to build a family very strongly because I lost my family when I was 15, 14, and I missed the family unit very much."', '"Family,Lost,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I was in Australia for many years. And the system there is a two-party system and the government changes from time to time.', '"Time,Government,Australia"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"We need to give the prime minister of the day a chance. If he or she cannot win an election, so be it. But no prime minister can push through the reforms we need if they cannot even finish a term in office."', '"Chance,Day,Election"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'To imagine a better life for yourself and your family and to leave behind all that is familiar requires a special kind of courage.', '"Life,Family,Courage"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'We are focusing too much on the problems and forgetting about the opportunities of immigration. Let us learn from our history. Immigration has been great for Australia in the past. I believe it will be great for Australia in the future.', '"Future,History,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I believe in a big Australia. I am an advocate for an ambitious immigration program.', '"Believe,I Am,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'Democracy needs to be nurtured and treated with care.', '"Democracy,Care,Needs"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"If I had stuck to my knitting, I would have had a wonderful career having a delicatessen in Blacktown."', '"Wonderful,Stuck,Knitting"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'All my life from a young man I have worked very hard and I enjoyed it very much and I was really afraid with what I would do when I no longer had the responsibility.', '"Life,Man,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I did a lot during my lifetime and I think it is time to make a change to my life at a young age of 87.', '"Life,Change,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'I have no fear about the future for retail investors.', '"Future,Fear,No Fear"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', 'It was very frustrating when I was president of Hakoah. You could not make any headway. We couldn\'t attract the public because it was an ethnic game. Australians were not interested.', '"Game,Not Interested,Ethnic"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"In football, in football clubs, there are many decisions that don\'t make business sense. Yes, there is always a lot of emotion involved."', '"Business,Football,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"The game needs to be funded by sponsors, by members, by broadcasters. There needs to be a commercial relationship between the FFA and the people who supply the money so it is a natural alliance. Sport is not a charity."', '"Money,Relationship,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3a', '"My family are big philanthropists, but not at putting big money into sport. Today sport is professional. It has to support itself or it won\'t exist. It cannot depend on a few wealthy people making donations."', '"Family,Money,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"A compelling story, even if factually inaccurate, can be more emotionally compelling than a dry recitation of the truth."', '"Truth,Story,More"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'The way you communicate an idea is different than the way you communicate a product.', '"Communication,Way,Product"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Some people call it global warming; some people call it climate change. What is the difference?', '"Change,People,Global Warming"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"Eighty percent of our life is emotion, and only 20 percent is intellect. I am much more interested in how you feel than how you think. I can change how you think, but how you feel is something deeper and stronger, and it\'s something that\'s inside you."', '"Life,Change,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"Republicans use think tanks to come up with a lot of their messages. The think tanks are the single worst, most undisciplined example of communication I\'ve ever seen."', '"Communication,Worst,Use"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"It is acceptable to bring someone to tears if it explains to them in an emotional way why a product, a service, or a candidate is the right person, is the right thing to do."', '"Service,Tears,Right Person"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"It\'s all emotion. But there\'s nothing wrong with emotion. When we are in love, we are not rational; we are emotional. When we are on vacation, we are not rational; we are emotional."', '"Love,Nothing,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"The challenge in working in politics, particularly if you\'re working for a political party, is that everyone\'s a messenger."', '"Politics,Political,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Preserving parks and open spaces is a winner because it doesn\'t need to be explained to everyday Americans.', '"Winner,Open,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"People like me have to have the discipline only to work for clients, corporations, political people, products, services, networks that we believe in and we want to see succeed."', '"Work,Discipline,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'There\'s a problem with political polling in that you have so much pressure to do what your client wants you to do and say what your client wants you to say. I\'ve never felt that pressure. I am independent of the political parties.', '"Politics,Political,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"I don\'t understand why people whose entire lives or their corporate success depends on communication, and yet they are led on occasion by CEOs who cannot talk their way out of a paper bag and don\'t care to."', '"Success,Communication,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'There\'s a lot of money with a lot of big law firms that have a tremendous amount at stake by getting the right language to convince the right jury that my client is either innocent or that the opposition is guilty.', '"Money,Law,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"One of the things that you have trouble with politicians, particularly in Washington, is when you get mad at them and you can\'t touch them; you can\'t punch them; you can\'t yell at them."', '"Politicians,Mad,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'The fundamental problem for Republicans when it comes to the environment is that whatever you say is viewed through the prism of suspicion.', '"Whatever,Through,Suspicion"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Sound science must be our guide in choosing which problems to tackle and how to approach them.', '"Science,Problems,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Politics is gut; commercials are gut.', '"Politics,Gut,Commercials"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"In fact, in more cases than not, when we are rational, we\'re actually unhappy. Emotion is good; passion is good. Being into what we\'re into, provided that it\'s a healthy pursuit, it\'s a good thing."', '"Good,Passion,Unhappy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'We decide based on how people look; we decide based on how people sound; we decide based on how people are dressed. We decide based on their passion.', '"Passion,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"The principles behind explaining and educating the product or the elected official is similar, even though the actual execution of it is very, very different."', '"Product,Execution,Principles"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"We as Americans assume that big companies are bad, and big power companies are even worse."', '"Power,Bad,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'I have seen how effective language attached to policies that are mainstream and delivered by people who are passionate and effective can change the course of history.', '"Change,History,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"The Republican National Committee hired me, and they hired me because they wanted someone who could look members straight in the eye and tell them the truth."', '"Truth,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"The language of America changed with the election of Bill Clinton, because with all due respect to my friends on the Republican side, Bill Clinton is the best communicator of the last 50 years. He felt your pain."', '"Best,Respect,Pain"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"Words can sometimes be used to confuse, but it\'s up to the practitioners of the study of language to apply them for good and not for evil. It is just like fire; fire can heat your house or burn it down."', '"Good,Fire,Heat"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"There are words that work, that are meant to explain and educate on policies that work, on products that work, on services that work. I\'m not going to ever try to sell a lemon. I don\'t do that."', '"Work,Words,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"So often corporate America, business America, are the worst communicators, because all they understand are facts, and they cannot tell a story. They know how to explain their quarterly results, but they don\'t know how to explain what they mean."', '"Business,Facts,America"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"When I started in this business, everybody said the Democrats were the better communicators because they sounded like social workers, and Republicans were awful because they sounded like morticians. In some cases. they actually dressed like morticians."', '"Business,Better,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"There are people still in the Republican Party that I believe practice the communication of anger, of disappointment, of regret, of pain, of sorrow, of suffering. That\'s not what the American people want to hear."', '"Communication,Anger,Pain"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"The advantage of working for a corporation is that it has only one message, because a product or a service doesn\'t speak; it\'s just there, and you can advertise it."', '"Service,Product,Speak"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'How I say it has as much of an impact on what people think of me as what I say.', '"Me,People,Impact"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('397999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'We as Americans and as humans have very selective hearing and very selective memory. We only hear what we want to hear and disregard the rest.', '"Rest,Memory,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Ideology and communication more often than not run into each other rather than complement each other. Principle and communication work together. Ideology and communication often work apart.', '"Work,Communication,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'What matters most in politics is personality. It\'s not issues; it\'s not image. It\'s who you are and what you represent.', '"Politics,Personality,Image"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'My job as a pollster is to understand what really matters.', '"Understand,Job,Matters"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"I\'ve done reasonably well over the last 10 years because I took the strategy of language and politics and applied it to the corporate world, which has never been done before."', '"Politics,World,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', '"If you\'re a good numbers person, you\'re a bad language person."', '"Good,Bad,Numbers"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3b', 'Traditional market researchers are cold and calculating and scientific.', '"Cold,Market,Scientific"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"Today and always, there will be an obligation to pass on to the new generation the tradition of liberal scholarship - scientific or in the humanities - and to bring the understanding of things and human actions to everyone."', '"Today,New,Generation"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"The production of antibody is not the only, nor I believe the most important, manifestation of immunity, but for reasons both historical and of experimental convenience, antibody is likely to remain the touchstone of immunological theory."', '"Believe,Important,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"Human insulin differs from other mammalian types by having a different C-terminal amino acid on the B chain. The immunological difference between beef insulin and human insulin, which is presumably responsible for the antigenicity of the former in some human beings, is thus limited to very a small portion of the whole molecule."', '"Difference,Small,Beef"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"To advance science is highly honourable, and I believe the institution of the Nobel Prizes has done much to raise the prestige of scientific discovery."', '"Science,Believe,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"I like to think that when Medawar and his colleagues showed that immunological tolerance could be produced experimentally, the new immunology was born."', '"Colleagues,New,Tolerance"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3c', '"Serum albumin is a well-defined protein, but no laboratory has yet attempted to ascertain its full chemical structure."', '"Protein,Laboratory,Chemical"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3d', '"I\'m a big fan of documentaries. I\'ve always loved them, and I\'ve just never had the opportunity or the time to make a feature."', '"Time,Opportunity,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3d', '"I love film, and I love seeing movies on film."', '"Love,Movies,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3d', '"When I made \'Eight Below,\' they wanted me to shoot digital, and I didn\'t want to do it because that\'s just what I need, to get a great series of takes and then find out the camera was frozen."', '"Great,Me,Digital"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'The sky is the limit. You never have the same experience twice.', '"Experience,Sky,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'Everyone has a story to tell. All you have to do is write it. But it\'s not that easy.', '"Easy,Everyone,Story"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'Happiness is hard to recall. Its just a glow.', '"Happiness,Glow,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"For some reason, I wrote about the bed we slept in when I was a kid. It was a half-acre of misery, that bed, sagging in the middle, red hair sticking out of the mattress, the spring gone and the fleas leaping all over the place."', '"Hair,Red,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I learned the significance of my own insignificant life.', '"Life,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"My father and mother should have stayed in New York, where they met and married and where I was born."', '"Father,New,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I look back on my childhood, I wonder how I survived at all."', '"Childhood,Look,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'There\'s so much absurdity. Poverty is so absurd.', '"Poverty,Absurd,Absurdity"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I think there\'s something about the Irish experience - that we had to have a sense of humor or die.', '"Experience,Humor,Die"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I was unloading sides of beef down on the docks when I decided enough was enough. By then, I\'d done a lot of reading on my own, so I persuaded New York University to enroll me."', '"Me,New,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I was a teacher, I\'d walk into the classroom. I stood at the board. I was the man. I directed operations. I was an intellectual and artistic and moral traffic cop, and I - and I would direct the class, most of the time."', '"Time,Teacher,Walk"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Way back in my mid-20s, I started making notes. I would just jot things down: lists of street names, songs, peculiar turns of speech, jokes, whatever."', '"Street,Way,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"If I had millions and millions and millions of dollars, I\'d leave a large portion to the 42nd Street library. That\'s why - that was my hangout, the reading rooms, the North and South reading rooms. I\'d go there, and my God, I couldn\'t believe I had access to all of these books. That was my university."', '"God,Believe,Street"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"On the last day of my teaching career, I was sitting in my apartment, having a glass of wine, thinking I\'m glad I did it, that I had been somehow useful, that I had learned something."', '"Thinking,Day,Glass"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I\'m not one of those James Joyce intellectuals who can stand back and look at the whole edifice... It was a slow process for me to just crawl out of it, like a snake leaving his skin behind."', '"Look,Snake,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I read about Joyce, I realised that there was no eight-till-one in his life: it was 24 hours a day for him."', '"Life,Day,24 Hours"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'Scatter my ashes on the Shannon.', '"Ashes,Scatter"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I certainly couldn\'t have written \'Angela\'s Ashes\' when my mother was alive, because she would have been ashamed."', '"Alive,Mother,She"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I became a teacher all right. I wanted to become a teacher because I had a misconception about it. I didn\'t know that I\'d be going into - when I first became a high school teacher in New York, that I\'d be going into a battle zone, and no one prepared me for that."', '"Teacher,Me,Battle"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'The happy childhood is hardly worth your while.', '"Childhood,Happy,Worth"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'Every life is a mystery. There is nobody whose life is normal and boring.', '"Life,Life Is A,Boring"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I had moments with my father that were exquisite - the stories he told me about Cuchulain, the mythological Irish warrior, are still magical to me."', '"Me,Father,Warrior"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"There was a kind of madness in the country. Eamon De Valera, the prime minister, had this vision of an Ireland where we\'d all be in some kind of native costume - which doesn\'t exist - and we\'d be dancing at the crossroads, babbling away in Gaelic, going to Mass, everyone virginal and pure."', '"Vision,Country,Madness"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Mam was always saying we had a simple diet: tea and bread, bread and tea, a liquid and a solid, a balanced diet - what more do you need? Nobody got fat."', '"Diet,Simple,Tea"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I never expected to write a book about a slum in Ireland that was going to catapult me, as they say, into some kind of - onto the best seller list."', '"Best,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"We had nothing, no television, no radio, nothing to get in the way. We read by the streetlight at the top of the lane, and we acted out the stories."', '"Way,Nothing,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"He came to the States in 1963, I think with a view to making up with my mother, but that didn\'t work. He came for three weeks, and drank his way all over Brooklyn. And went back... I went to his funeral in Belfast."', '"Work,View,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Kids all want to look cool, as if knowledge is a great burden, but they\'re always looking around. They remember."', '"Cool,Knowledge,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Something happened when the memoirs of so-called ordinary people, like myself, suddenly hit the bestseller list."', '"Myself,People,Happened"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I thought everything would be different in America. It wasn\'t.', '"America,Everything,Be Different"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"You sail into the harbor, and Staten Island is on your left, and then you see the Statue of Liberty. This is what everyone in the world has dreams of when they think about New York. And I thought, \'My God, I\'m in Heaven. I\'ll be dancing down Fifth Avenue like Fred Astaire with Ginger Rogers.\'"', '"Dreams,God,World"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Certain citizens claimed I had disgraced the fair name of the city of Limerick, that I had attacked the church, that I had despoiled my mother\'s name, and that if I returned to Limerick, I would surely be found hanging from a lamppost."', '"City,Church,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Worse than the ordinary, miserable childhood is the miserable Irish childhood, and worse yet is the miserable Irish Catholic childhood."', '"Childhood,Miserable,Worse"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I couldn\'t fit in the Irish community in New York. I was never one of the boys because they would talk about baseball or basketball, and I knew nothing about it."', '"Community,New,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I didn\'t have to struggle at all to get an agent and a publisher. Everything fell into my lap.', '"Struggle,Everything,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"A lot of people say writers start losing their powers after 60 or 65. But I look at the best-seller list and see a book by that 14-year-old gymnast, Dominique Moceanu, and I think, \'Now, what\'s she going to tell the world? And these 25-year-old rock stars, what are they going to tell the world?\'"', '"Look,Stars,World"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"My mother had had six children in five and a half years, and three of them died in that time."', '"Time,Children,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Sure, I went through my \'J\'accuse\' phase. I was so angry for so long, I could hardly have a conversation without getting into an argument. And it was only when I felt I could finally distance myself from my past that I began to write about what happened - not just to me, but to lots of young people. I think my story is a cautionary tale."', '"Myself,Angry,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I think that\'s why you see so many Americans in Dublin look so sad: they are looking for the door through which they can begin to understand this place. I tell them, \'Go to the races.\' I think it\'s the best place to start understanding the Irish."', '"Best,Sad,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I just have to proceed as usual. No matter what happens, nothing helps with the writing of the next book."', '"Nothing,Matter,Next"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"You feel a sense of urgency, especially at my advanced age, when you\'re staring into the grave."', '"Age,Feel,Urgency"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I\'ve been writing in notebooks for 40 years or so.', '"Writing,Been,Notebooks"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'First of all there is always that artistic challenge of creating something. Or the particular experience to take slum life in that period and make something out of it in the form of a book. And then I felt some kind of responsibility to my family.', '"Life,Family,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"My childhood here... was very limited. So it was a long, long time before I actually went out to Brooklyn."', '"Time,Childhood,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"And, of course, they\'ve always condemned dancing. You know, you might touch a member of the opposite sex. And you might get excited and you might do something natural."', '"Sex,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I had no accomplishments except surviving. But that isn\'t enough in the community where I came from, because everybody was doing it. So I wasn\'t prepared for America, where everybody is glowing with good teeth and good clothes and food."', '"Good,Food,Community"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I had to get rid of any idea of hell or any idea of the afterlife. That\'s what held me, kept me down. So now I just have nothing but contempt for the institution of the church."', '"Me,Hell,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I admire certain priests and nuns who go off on their own and do God\'s work on their own, who help in the ghettos, but as far as the institution of the church is concerned, I think it is despicable."', '"Work,God,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Actually, my mother and Alfie came for three weeks\' Christmas vacation and stayed for 21 years. I guess my mother never went back because she was lonely."', '"Christmas,Back,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"They all went into the bar business. Which was a mistake, because they began to sip at the merchandise and it set them back, set us all back. Well, them more than I."', '"Business,Mistake,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I\'m more interested in writing than in performing.', '"More,Writing,Interested"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'The main thing I am interested in is my experience as a teacher.', '"Experience,Teacher,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I can\'t go too much into my domestic life because there are ex-wives ready to do me in.', '"Life,Me,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I think I settled on the title before I ever wrote the book.', '"Think,Book,Title"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'We never really had any kind of a Christmas. This is one part where my memory fails me completely.', '"Christmas,Me,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"If somebody wants me to speak in, say, Chicago, a limousine picks me up at the door to brings me to the airport. I fly at the front of the plane, and a limousine meets me at the other end to take me to a grand hotel, and usually an envelope is left for me with a per diem, maybe $150-a-day walking around money, and then I go home."', '"Money,Home,Fly"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"If ever you are to be visited by the Holy Ghost, you should make certain you\'re sitting beside a fireman."', '"Sitting,Holy,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"We were supposed to stay over in Boston, but when Scribners heard I\'d won the Pulitzer, they told me to get on a plane - that Katie Couric wanted my body. And when Katie Couric wants your body, you get moving right away."', '"Me,Body,Moving"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'They tell me I\'m on \'Politically Incorrect\' with Ollie North. That should be a lot of fun.', '"Me,Fun,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"It\'s like a series of waves hitting you. First, getting excerpted in the \'New Yorker\' last summer, then getting published, then the best-seller list, the award, the movie deal, now this, a Pulitzer."', '"Award,Summer,New"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I first went up to see my editor, I was with my agent, and my editor said, \'Well, what have you been doing all these years?\' And my agent said, \'He\'s been in recovery. From his childhood.\'"', '"Childhood,See,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I was a kid, I was a pretty good runner, and there was nothing like winning a race."', '"Good,Winning,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I came to America, I dreamed bigger dreams."', '"Dreams,America,Bigger"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I loved reading and writing, and teaching was the most exalted profession I could imagine."', '"Loved,Imagine,Writing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Early in my teaching days, the kids asked me the meaning of a poem. I replied, \'I don\'t know any more than you do. I have ideas. What are your ideas?\' I realized then that we\'re all in the same boat. What does anybody know?"', '"Boat,Me,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I think there are two cities in the world - New York and Rome.', '"World,New,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"You look at passers-by in Rome and think, \'Do they know what they have here?\' You can say the same about Philadelphia. Do people know what went on here?"', '"Look,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'One day a week should be set aside for field trips.', '"Day,Week,One Day"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"There were a number of houses. When we first arrived in Limerick, it was a one-room affair with most of it taken up with a bed."', '"Bed,First,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I didn\'t know you could write about yourself. Nobody ever told me about this.', '"Me,Yourself,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'O\'Casey was writing about people in the streets and his mother and dying babies and poverty. So that astounded me because I thought you could only write about English matters.', '"Me,People,Poverty"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I was a houseman, the lowest. I was just above - in the hierarchy of jobs, I was just above the Puerto Rican dishwashers - just above, so I felt superior to them."', '"Above,Just,Superior"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"St. Patrick, bringing the religion to Ireland, this is what we should celebrate."', '"Religion,Celebrate,Ireland"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"That\'s what kept us going - a sense of absurdity, rather than humor."', '"Humor,Us,Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I\'m a late bloomer.', '"Late,Late Bloomer,Bloomer"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"At 66, you\'re supposed to die or get hemorrhoids."', '"Die,Get,Supposed"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I just wrote the book and was amazed and astounded that it became a bestseller and won the Pulitzer Prize. It still hasn\'t sunk in.', '"Book,Just,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"For some reason, I had a responsibility to my family and the people who lived around me. I felt that I had to convey their dignity - the way they dealt with adversity and poverty - and their good humor."', '"Family,Good,Humor"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'A funeral was a great form of entertainment. A wake was a great form of entertainment.', '"Great,Entertainment,Funeral"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Ireland, once you live there, you\'re seduced by it."', '"Live,Once,Ireland"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"We don\'t look at teachers as scholars the way they do in Europe. In Spain you\'re called a professor if you\'re a high school teacher, and they pay teachers - they pay teachers in Europe."', '"Teacher,Look,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"When I got out of the army, I had the G.I. Bill. Since I had no high school education or anything like that, I came to NYU, and they took a chance on me and let me in."', '"Education,Chance,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I would dream of going up to the \'New York Times\' and asking them if I could please be a copy boy or let me scrub the toilets or something like that. But I couldn\'t rise to those heights.', '"Me,New,Rise"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I can do no more than tell the truth.', '"Truth,I Can,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'People who think I have insulted Ireland or Limerick or my family have not read the book!', '"Family,People,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'The uncluttered life is the key to a good memory.', '"Life,Good,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I was just dreaming, and if, if I\'d written the book and nobody wanted it, I would have put it in the drawer and said, \'Well, I did that.\'"', '"Nobody,Well,Said"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I don\'t know anything about a stock!', '"Know,Anything,About"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"The part of Limerick we lived in is Georgian, you know, those Georgian houses. You see them in pictures of Dublin."', '"See,Know,Pictures"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'My sister died in Brooklyn.', '"Sister,Brooklyn,Died"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I worked in a number of high schools in New York, and I wound up at Stuyvesant High School, which is known nationally for producing brilliant scientists and mathematicians, but I had writing classes. I thought I was teaching. They thought I was teaching, but I was learning."', '"Learning,New,School"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I never really fit in anywhere.', '"Never,Anywhere,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Even when I went to the Lion\'s Head in the Village, where all you journalists would hang out, I was always peripheral. I was never really part of anything except the classroom. That\'s where I belonged."', '"Village,Lion,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'There\'s nothing in the world like getting up in front of a high-school classroom in New York City. They won\'t give you a break if you don\'t hold them. There\'s no escape.', '"World,City,Escape"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Just luxuriate in a certain memory, and the details will come. It\'s like a magnet attracting steel filings."', '"Memory,Details,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'People come up to me and talk about the alcoholism in their family.', '"Family,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'We\'ve had enough of the generals and movie stars. We want to hear about the ordinary people.', '"Stars,People,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"In public schools, classes are bloated - it\'s ridiculous."', '"Ridiculous,Public,Bloated"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"My dream was to have a Library of Congress catalogue number, that\'s all."', '"Library,Congress,Dream"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'We were below welfare. We begged from people on welfare. My father tried to repair our shoes with pieces of bicycle tires.', '"Bicycle,Shoes,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I had never attended high school, but I was fairly well read."', '"School,Never,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I was ashamed of it, of the poverty I came from."', '"Poverty,Ashamed,I Came"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I\'ve had experiences on both sides of the ocean and various classrooms and bedrooms around New York.', '"New,Ocean,Sides"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"If I have a cause, it\'s the cause of the teacher."', '"Teacher,Cause"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Some, like Mother Teresa, are born with a gene to help the poor, and some are born with a gene to write. I was born with a gene to tell my story, and I just had to."', '"Poor,Help,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"It gives me a very keen satisfaction that, after listening to my blather all those years, former students are now seeing that I wrote a book, that I did have it in me."', '"Me,Satisfaction,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I knew I had to find my own way of teaching.', '"Way,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'I hated school in Ireland.', '"School,Ireland,Hated"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"You don\'t have to go fight bulls in Spain like Hemingway to write something great, or go off to war. It\'s right under your nose."', '"War,Great,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Teachers have a million stories, but nobody consults them."', '"Nobody,Teachers,Million"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I couldn\'t even pick up the newspaper without saying, \'This is a fine piece of writing. I wish to hell I could write like this.\'"', '"Hell,Wish,Newspaper"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I\'m always a great student of writers\' work habits. Balzac sat at his desk dressed in a monk\'s robe, and he always had to have a rotten apple on his desk. The smell of the apple inspired him somehow."', '"Work,Great,Smell"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'The day I write my last word will be the day that I feel free.', '"Free,Day,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"If you have a class of 35 children, and they\'re all smiling, and there\'s one little bastard, and he\'s just staring at you as if to say \'Show me\', then he\'s the one you think about going home on the train."', '"Home,Me,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I don\'t see myself as either Irish or American, I\'m a New Yorker."', '"Myself,New,See"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"I wanted to avoid all that literary stuff. I didn\'t want the self pity of \'The Portrait,\' all the moaning and the whingeing. I\'m not knocking Joyce: we all owe him a debt. He\'s the one who made so much possible."', '"Portrait,Self,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'People want real-life stories.', '"People,Want,Stories"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', 'You\'re beginning to hear the tale of the common man and woman rather than the traditional memoir about the generals who just finished the war or the politicians who just rendered glorious service to the country.', '"War,Man,Service"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3e', '"Autobiography should be more stringent. It should adhere more to the standards of journalism - assuming that journalism has the truth. The memoir gives you more scope, is more poetic, and allows you to play around with your own life."', '"Life,Truth,Journalism"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'The noir hero is a knight in blood caked armor. He\'s dirty and he does his best to deny the fact that he\'s a hero the whole time.', '"Best,Time,Hero"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"When you have a brush in your hand, inking a beautiful woman is a lot like running your hands over her."', '"Beautiful Woman,Beautiful,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'Sometimes the solitary voice can be the best one.', '"Best,Sometimes,Voice"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I\'m a comic book artist. So I think to myself, what do I like to draw? I like to draw hot chicks, fast cars and cool guys in trench coats. So that\'s what I write about."', '"Cool,Myself,Hot"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I grew up on the crime stuff. Spillane, Chandler, Jim Thompson, and noir movies like Fuller, Orson Welles, Fritz Lang. When I first showed up in New York to write comics back in the late 1970s, I came with a bunch of crime stories but everybody just wanted men in tights."', '"Men,Movies,New"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"The Spartans were a paradoxical people. They were the biggest slave owners in Greece. But at the same time, Spartan women had an unusual level of rights. It\'s a paradox that they were a bunch of people who in many ways were fascist, but they were the bulwark against the fall of democracy."', '"Women,Time,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"What\'s happened with computer technology is perfectly timed for someone with my set of skills. I tell stories with pictures. What I love about CGI is that if I can think it, it can be put on the screen."', '"Love,Technology,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I thought Daredevil was kind of cool because he couldn\'t do anything. I mean, he\'s blind. It wasn\'t that he could fly. His major power was an impediment. So I was intrigued. When I took over he was kind of like Spider-Man-lite, but I was able to project a lot of my Catholic imagery onto it. And I\'d always wanted to do a crime comic."', '"Cool,Power,Fly"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"\'Comic book\' has come to mean a specific genre, not a story form, in people\'s minds. So someone will call \'Die Hard\' a \'comic-book movie,\' when it has nothing to do with comic books. I\'d rather have comics be the vehicle by which stories are told."', '"Die,People,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"The comics I read as a kid were all about guys in tights. But here was a guy who wore a fedora. He fought crime like they did in Marvel and DC, but he did it in the real world. I had just turned 12 when I met the Spirit and it was a strange coincidence. At the same time I discovered girls I fell out of love with guys in tights."', '"Love,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'You can\'t have virtue without sin. What I\'m after is having my characters\' virtues defined by how they operate in a very sinful environment. That\'s how you test people.', '"People,Virtues,Sin"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'I\'m a spoilt brat. I thought I was just going to walk in and make movies. But I\'d been my own boss for so long that all of a sudden to be facing a roomful of people who were niggling over every little scene... I just thought I\'d go back and draw my comics and have a happy life.', '"Life,Movies,Walk"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"When you think of what Americans accomplished, building these amazing cities and all the good it\'s done in the world, it\'s kind of disheartening to hear so much hatred of America, not just from abroad, but internally."', '"Good,Amazing,World"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'What I want to bring back to superheroes with this project is a sense of play. Things have gotten so dreary. The heroes have gotten so ugly that even their muscles have muscles.', '"Back,Ugly,Project"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"You do Batman right, and he\'s going to be popular. He\'s a great character. I was once asked by somebody if writing \'Batman\' was like holding a Ming vase or something. And I said, \'No, it\'s like holding a big-ass diamond that you can\'t break. You can throw him against the ceiling, against the floor, anywhere, and you just can\'t break Batman.\'"', '"Great,Character,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"In a way, \'Sin City\'s designed to be paced somewhere between an American comic book and Japanese manga. Working in black and white, I realized that the eye is less patient, and you have to make your point, and sometimes repeat it. Slowing things down is harder in black and white, because there isn\'t as much for the eye to enjoy."', '"Black And White,Black,City"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"The larger-than-life thing is definitely what I\'m after. I\'ve always drawn dark stories. Occasionally, I\'ll try a perfect hero, but it\'s a real stretch for me. I like \'em warts and all, and obsessive and weird."', '"Hero,Me,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"My feeling is that the hero has now been defined by phrases like the odious one that we were all raised with - crimes does not pay. Of course it pays, you schmuck. That\'s not why we don\'t do it. We don\'t do it because it is wrong."', '"Hero,Why,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'Hollywood is a town; it\'s not a medium. And cinema is a medium you can practice anywhere.', '"Cinema,Practice,Hollywood"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"\'Occupy\' is nothing but a pack of louts, thieves, and rapists, an unruly mob, fed by Woodstock-era nostalgia and putrid false righteousness. These clowns can do nothing but harm America."', '"America,Nostalgia,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"We\'re constantly told that all cultures are equal, and that every belief system is as good as the next. And it led to a kind of - and generally, that America was to be known for its flaws rather than its virtues."', '"Good,Flaws,America"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I don\'t own an ounce of the work I\'ve ever done on \'Batman,\' and I still work on \'Batman.\' I love the character, I think it\'s a lot of fun, and it\'s kind of fun to be in that ballpark every once in a while, where you\'re seeing a different crowd."', '"Love,Work,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"Mighty cultures never - are almost never conquered. They crumble from within. And frankly, I think that a lot of Americans are acting like spoiled brats because everything isn\'t working out perfectly every time."', '"Time,Acting,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I will throw all my best efforts into it, my thoughts and political observations, but ultimately I want to create a narrative that keeps you turning the pages and leaves you with a sense that this thing has a reason for being there."', '"Best,Thoughts,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'Think of me as the weathered sheriff coming back into Dodge \'cause the youngsters are shooting up the church and scaring the horses and not doing right by the women.', '"Women,Me,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I realized that I was about to turn 30, and Batman was permanently 29. And I was going to be damned if I was older than Batman."', '"Turn,About,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"I think most things I read on the Internet and in newspapers are propaganda. Everyone from the \'New York Times\' to Rupert Murdoch has a point of view and is putting forth their own propaganda. They\'re stuck with the facts as they are, but the way they interpret and frame them is wildly different."', '"View,Internet,Facts"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'It is more raw and unfettered and I\'m more likely going into something you could call extreme cartooning. There\'s a lot of that in the course of \'Holy Terror.\' There are interludes where there are pictures - cartoon pictures - of modern figures and they are all wordless. It\'s up to readers to put the words in.', '"Words,Cartoon,More"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'I don\'t do a comic book thinking there is a movie. I just want it to be as good a comic book as it can be.', '"Good,Thinking,Comic"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'Cartoonists\' dirty secret is that we tend to come up with stories that involve things that are really fun to draw.', '"Fun,Dirty,Secret"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', 'But I\'m not trying to convince anybody how to vote or how to live. Nobody\'s ever successfully accused me of being realistic.', '"Me,Live,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"3,000 of my neighbors were murdered. My country was, utterly unprovoked, savagely attacked. I wish all those responsible for the atrocity of 9/11 to burn in Hell."', '"Hell,Country,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"It was said Daredevil grew up in Hell\'s Kitchen, an amazing name for a neighbourhood. But that opened a Pandora\'s box of all the crime stuff I wanted to do. I borrowed liberally from Will Eisner\'s \'The Spirit\' and turned \'Daredevil\' into a crime comic."', '"Amazing,Hell,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"In the comic-book world, there tends to be an overblown sense of tradition. Bad habits die hard. There are ways I think the form could work more effectively if we lost the bad habits that were created before we were born."', '"Work,World,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"Comics are so full of amazing work. And I can\'t look at a drawing of a woman without thinking of, for instance, Wallace Wood and his amazing way of capturing beauty."', '"Beauty,Work,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"As a cartoonist, I\'m a caricaturist. First you find out what somebody really looks like, and then you find out what they \'really\' look like."', '"Look,Find,Looks"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"Comic-book pages are vertical, and movie screens are relentlessly horizontal. But it\'s all the same form. We use different tools, but we get the job done. I\'m completely in love with CGI. It\'s great for conveying a cartoonist\'s sense of reality."', '"Love,Great,Reality"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe3f', '"Where I would fault President Bush the most was that, in the wake of 9/11, he motivated our military, but he didn\'t call the nation into a state of war. And he didn\'t explain that this would take though a communal effort against common foe."', '"War,Effort,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think Matt Mitrione is a super tough guy, very athletic but I think that I\'d probably get more pay-per-view buys if I fought Fedor."', '"Tough,Tough Guy,More"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"To have an effective striking match, you need gloves on. Junior dos Santos would have a very short career if he was in a bare knuckle fight. The early UFCs, before gloves, were grappling with some striking."', '"Fight,Need,Match"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'ve been training in martial arts since I was a baby running around the school. Everything from wrestling to muay thai. I started wrestling when I was 15.', '"Training,School,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"By training with Ken Hahn, who comes from that full-contact karate school where he\'s hitting me in the back of the head while I\'m hitting the bag, I learned that pain is a temporary state."', '"Pain,Me,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'It has always been a dream of mine to fight in Japan.', '"Fight,Always,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think the day of retirement will come when I go out there and do everything I was supposed to do and I still can\'t perform. I\'m going out there and I\'m a danger to myself, then it stresses your family out."', '"Family,Myself,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I don\'t want them to have to be the one to come tell me, \'Hey, you performing at the top of your sport is no longer feasible. Biology has set its course.\'"', '"Me,Biology,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"At least my situation I can be like, look, I avoid physical confrontations, obviously not because I have an issue with physical violence, but I try to see the bigger picture of what it takes for humans to coincide with each other. We\'re all the same race."', '"Look,Picture,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"You always see the guys who go, \'Walk away from a fight,\' and people look at him and go, \'You\'re not really a fighter anyways. Are you walking away because you\'re strong or because of your cowardice?\'"', '"Walk,Fight,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"In the future, I\'d like to break more into acting and stuff. I think that pro wrestling is a great springboard, really. You see a lot of guys coming from that world. In a lot of ways, it\'s like live theater. Guys going out there and performing and having to act on the fly and be their own stuntmen at the same time."', '"Future,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I very much like the Japanese version of pro wrestling, probably the most."', '"Version,Like,Pro"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'ve watched guys in pro wrestling actually die. It\'s very dangerous. It\'s very injury heavy.', '"Die,Dangerous,Injury"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I fought Mark Hunt and I got caught with a shot that he threw. That\'s kind of like getting caught by a submission by me.', '"Me,Shot,He"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'The margin for error with Mark Hunt is a lot smaller than it is with some of the other heavyweights where you can get caught with a shot and maybe recover.', '"Shot,Error,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I didn\'t have anything to prove to begin with to anybody else. I didn\'t start out doing this because I wanted to win awards or titles. I like martial arts, I like training, I like the lifestyle."', '"Training,Start,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I want to constantly get better. Why not just keep fighting? Until I get told that I can\'t anymore, then I\'ll move on."', '"Fighting,Better,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"At first, when I hit 300 pounds, my wife actually brought that up. She said, \'You do realize you can\'t walk around like this if you want to train or fight. It doesn\'t look like you want to fight anymore. Do you want to fight?\' That called into question my own reality."', '"Walk,Fight,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think just being in there with Fedor is an impressive thing to be able to say at the end of my career, sitting in my office telling people my accolades."', '"People,End,Sitting"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Who you fought is a test of who you really are.', '"Test,Who,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Someone who sees you on a certain night, maybe they\'ve seen you on a bad night. I\'ve seen Tom Brady throw interceptions. Is it time to retire, or is it a bad game? What if all week in practice he looked phenomenal?"', '"Time,Night,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Fedor is kind of hard to nail down to one company.', '"Company,Hard,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If I get too political or if I say things... the whole religious thing, which if you know my background, kind of baffles me anyway. I leave that to the people that are religious and that\'s their thing. I just try to steer clear of it."', '"Political,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Competing is something that once I retire from, it\'s not something I can go back and do."', '"Back,I Can,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'d rather fight named fighters and Fedor\'s somebody I\'ve always wanted to fight and I think that it would be nice to be able to complete that kind of Who\'s Who of my resume.', '"Fight,Always,Be Nice"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I enjoy fighting.', '"Fighting,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I want to fight for as long as possible.', '"Fight,Long,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I never found striking to be an effective form of fighting. I still clown people and tell them how animals in the wild that are hunted, they have to strike, bulls and rams, they use striking as protective nature. But the ones who are the predators, they\'re the grapplers who go for the throat."', '"Nature,Fighting,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'ve always been a fan of martial arts, even before I did jiu-jitsu tournaments. I did point karate tournaments and wrestled in high school. To me, it was just an evolution and mixed martial arts was the next step. I just wanted to compete and train in it. I had no illusions of it being a paying gig."', '"Me,Step,School"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I watched guys who were professional fighters hit each other 30 times, and it still didn\'t go anywhere. I thought \'that wasn\'t very effective\' But I saw if you got someone in a choke, you can end a fight in seconds, and I pushed toward that."', '"Fight,End,Professional"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I love martial arts, so why wouldn\'t I want to help people understand it more?"', '"Love,People,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think the more that people appreciate the sport, the more they\'re a fan of it."', '"People,More,Fan"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I remember one time watching Jose Aldo fight Jonathan Brookins, and he just chopped him up."', '"Time,Fight,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"There are too many fights in our sport that are exciting, and you\'ve got to let us fight."', '"Fight,Us,Exciting"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'m not an unintelligent individual.', '"Individual,Unintelligent"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Knowledge is just how I am. I like to know things. I\'m an inquisitive human being.', '"Knowledge,I Am,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'ve been a pretty big guy my whole life.', '"Life,Big,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'m pretty well-spoken guy, but I don\'t have a college education. Me making money in other avenues is not going to be as easy as walking into the Octagon."', '"Education,Money,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"He doesn\'t like to be hit. Not that anybody likes to be hit, but Brock for whatever reason has shown much more of a dramatic response to the negativity of those shots. To the point where he\'s not asleep, it isn\'t like he got knocked out, he\'s not getting dropped, but he just turns his face away from adversity."', '"Face,Adversity,Negativity"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Stipe is a phenomenal champ as far as like he\'s a good guy, if you want to point your kids in the right direction, \'Hey, look at this guy, he\'s a good person.\'"', '"Good,Look,Good Person"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I haven\'t fought the easiest opponents. You can show up at your best and still not come out on top.', '"Best,Your,Top"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"When people are wary about fighting on the ground, I have a more difficult time."', '"Time,Fighting,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'m all for CM Punk becoming a part of the organization. I think his background and training in martial arts, he should be capable of handling himself and doing well. And bottom line is, people are going to tune in to watch and that\'s pretty much the bar of getting into the UFC, if you can sell tickets."', '"Training,Organization,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Those guys at AKA know how to make adjustments.', '"Know,Make,How"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"In the past, I would try to use as little strength as possible because strength will get you tired if you explode too many times. Well, get in shape."', '"Strength,Tired,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"When people are pushing me against the cage, in the past I was more susceptible to allowing it to happen because I had that jiu-jitsu mentality that I\'m not going to grind back."', '"Me,Past,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"With the half-guard and guard, if you have a belly it\'s hard to pull your knees up."', '"Hard,Your,Belly"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"The dieting thing, I think you have to approach as intelligently as you can. First I started as a vegetarian. And for a whole year, I gave it a shot. And it kept my weight down. But honestly, my body fat wasn\'t as low - I got a little bit softer. I was getting injured a lot more. I felt a lack of \'umph.\'"', '"Fat,Body,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'ve been around long enough to know that you never say never.', '"Long,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I respect Brock, all the other fighters, and the sport of mixed martial arts."', '"Respect,Mixed,Sport"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Anderson Silva I think is extraordinarily talented, but I don\'t think his submission game is great. We\'ve seen him get caught in heel hooks."', '"Great,Game,Seen"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Georges St. Pierre has the best takedowns and dominant wrestling ability, and he\'s a great athlete, but he\'s shown he can be knocked out. I think B.J. Penn is the better fighter. He\'s the great martial artist."', '"Best,Great,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Brock Lesnar will never be able to beat me because he has no submission skills. What\'s he going to do, knock me out?"', '"Me,Will,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Fedor has great killer instinct, he\'s tough, he\'s strong. If I fought him I\'d try to catch him in a submission, but I don\'t know if Fedor can be beaten."', '"Great,Tough,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'As a martial artist you have to be truthful about yourself so you can approach your training properly and get better.', '"Yourself,Training,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I was having multiple surgeries after fights and not really addressing them the way I should have and having a proper off-season. So it was leading to more injuries and really making a strong influence on the way I was fighting. I was having to fight around injuries and not fight because it was the most efficient technique to use.', '"Fight,Fighting,Influence"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"No one is guaranteed a spot at the top, no one is guaranteed a title shot, but all you can do is win your fight, keep training, and then maybe somewhere down the road you\'ll get your opportunity."', '"Opportunity,Fight,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"People don\'t usually have long careers as heavyweights because they mature into the role. Look at amateur wrestling, you don\'t usually see guys go to heavyweight as freshman. I was just blessed that even though I wasn\'t as big as some of the other guys, I was able to step in right away at heavyweight."', '"Look,Long,Step"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'m a terrible actor.', '"Terrible,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"There are two ways I would consider retirement. One is losing to guys who are not top-level competition. The other is if I started losing where it\'s like, \'OK man, you were knocked out viciously and staring at the rafters.\' I won\'t endanger my health."', '"Health,Man,Competition"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"You could have 20 wins in a row, and if you lose your next one, you suck now, according to how the fans are."', '"Lose,Fans,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"In the UFC, you are only as good as your last fight. It\'s really a fight-by-fight type of career in the UFC."', '"Good,Fight,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'The fight ahead of you is always your most important one.', '"Fight,Important,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think other fighters can see that I\'ve had hardships, in and out of the cage, and I\'ve persevered and pushed forward. If other people can take that and incorporate it into their lives, then obviously that is rewarding for me to see."', '"Me,Hardships,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"It was always a goal of mine to go back to Cuba, where my paternal lineage comes from."', '"Back,Always,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"When it comes to wrestling, judo and boxing they are at a good level. They can compete in an international level. On the amateur level it is extremely high. Transitioning to MMA for them would be easy. I think we will see a lot more Cubans in MMA as it gets easier for them to complete."', '"Good,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Honestly, I think big guys are easier to fight. They don\'t move as fast, they get tired quickly and they\'re not as technical."', '"Fight,Tired,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I am one of the very few fighters who doesn\'t read any type of media.', '"I Am,Media,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I thought about 205 for awhile, particular when I was doing the Vegan diet and walking around at about 250lbs. I was counting calories and was serious about whether it was a possibility, but it\'s just not for me."', '"Diet,Me,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Having my own gym is easier because I have my family here, my kids enjoy watching my practices and I like having them around. It\'s hard to go to other people\'s gyms because not everyone if as kid-friendly as I am."', '"Family,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'m not going to question Brock\'s legitimacy.', '"Question,Going,Legitimacy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Even I didn\'t think I could beat Nogueira.', '"Beat,Think,Even"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"A lot of individuals are so worried about being politically correct. I\'d rather go ahead and say what\'s on my mind than to sit there and come up with some PC \'Oh, the guy is a great fighter and I have a lot of respect for him.\' If I don\'t mean it, why is it even coming out of my mouth?"', '"Respect,Great,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I want to fight Lesnar. I hate who he is as a person.', '"Fight,Hate,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I was suspended for two years and I got really fat. That was a polite way of putting it.', '"Fat,Way,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"There\'s guys that wish they were you, so they hate you for being you. And if you add the fact that you\'re well-spoken and good-looking... man, I got a lot of people that don\'t like me."', '"Hate,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'Indifference is what death is for us as fighters.', '"Death,Us,Indifference"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'You have to know how to move properly. A lot of these heavyweights go out there and they\'re fighting like it\'s a street fight. They\'re trying to win in the first 30 seconds.', '"Fight,Fighting,Street"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If you fight improperly, you can be in great shape, run marathons, swim 200 meters and I can still gas you in two minutes of a fight. If you don\'t know how to fight, it doesn\'t matter."', '"Great,Fight,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'ve trained in wing chung, jeet kune do, I\'ve indulged in many arts that people would not have thought I have trained in and incorporated."', '"People,Would,Thought"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"All my kids will train in martial arts; it\'s a requirement. Do I want them to fight professionally? Hell no. If they ever step into a cage, I\'ll cry. I would rather my daughter and sons be doctors and lawyers or wear a suit to work and use their brain and after work go train at the gym and spar hard."', '"Work,Fight,Brain"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Different martial arts have ways of showing you how to control an opponent and put him down, but jiu-jitsu is the king of how to finish somebody. And that\'s what I love about it."', '"Love,King,Control"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"The sport has to be entertaining, it has to make money. CM Punk brings that."', '"Money,Punk,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I love leg locks and heel hooks and kneebars. They\'re complex and hard to avoid.', '"Love,Hard,Avoid"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"For my striking, I\'ve learned to adapt it right off the bat for MMA. Even my jiu-jitsu, I adapt it very much for MMA."', '"Bat,Right,Adapt"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'ve finished fights from my feet, I\'ve finished fights with my ground-and-pound, and I\'ve finished fights from my back with a submission, from top with submission. You name it, and I\'ve finished a fight that way."', '"Fight,Feet,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I think it would be much easier to submit Mark Hunt than to knock him out. The guy has a pretty good chin, he\'s not the easiest of guys to put away."', '"Good,Pretty,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I\'m going to work on finishing Mark Hunt, but he\'s very hard to hold down. I feel like that\'s the best opportunity for victory for me."', '"Work,Best,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I don\'t perform well when my family isn\'t around me.', '"Family,Me,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'It\'s a disadvantage when there is not enough footage of an opponent.', '"Enough,Opponent,Disadvantage"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Growing up in Vegas there is that complaint that we have no sports team. We have boxing, but no boxers are ever from Vegas, they\'re always from the east."', '"Sports,Always,Boxing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If you don\'t hit hard and you weigh 260 pounds, that is something to worry about."', '"Worry,Hard,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If you break down actual techniques and knowledge of MMA, I am more knowledgeable than the head coaches of all the guys I\'m fighting. Forget the guys I\'m fighting. Obviously I know more than they do, nobody is going to question that. But I also know more than the guys who are teaching them about fighting. I could teach them."', '"Knowledge,I Am,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"I just love fighting. You lock me in there with another guy - that strategy, that game of chess - I\'m in love with it. I\'ll be in love with it until the day I die. Now, if you want to strap a belt on me at the end of it? That\'s cool, my kids can brag about it."', '"Love,Cool,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"Whenever I do something in life, I take it as far as I can take it. A lot of people think the easy road is to avoid adversity. But trust me, when you\'re an old man, you\'re not going to remember why you didn\'t do those things."', '"Life,Trust,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I\'ve been able to overcome obstacles that would fold most people over.', '"People,Obstacles,Overcome"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If you look at a lot of the best kicking footwork in the sport, karate has a huge influence. You can\'t be effective with it if you don\'t apply it correctly, however. You look at Conor McGregor, who is known for his boxing, but when I watch him fight I see a lot of karate movement with how he goes in and out."', '"Best,Fight,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"If you were to get a seminar in MMA, I think you\'d want one from me over Mark Hunt. I\'m more efficient and my understanding of the art is deeper, and I\'m still only growing in terms of my intelligence in combat."', '"Art,Intelligence,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', 'I have an ability to overcome adversity. I\'ve got a toughness that helps.', '"Adversity,Overcome,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"For some reason I didn\'t have a lot of social skills, I didn\'t date a lot of girls. I always had the thing where I was in love with one girl."', '"Love,Always,Girl"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe40', '"When I was 22, I had the opportunity to work as a bouncer. I only had to work one or two nights and could make enough money to spend the rest of my time training."', '"Work,Money,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'Cast your cares on God; that anchor holds.', '"God,Anchor,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'Every improvement in communication makes the bore more terrible.', '"Communication,Improvement,More"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'I know of no more disagreeable situation than to be left feeling generally angry without anybody in particular to be angry at.', '"Anger,Angry,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"Every man ought to be inquisitive through every hour of his great adventure down to the day when he shall no longer cast a shadow in the sun. For if he dies without a question in his heart, what excuse is there for his continuance?"', '"Great,Heart,Shadow"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'We do not mind our not arriving anywhere nearly so much as our not having any company on the way.', '"Mind,Way,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"A \'new thinker\', when studied closely, is merely a man who does not know what other people have thought."', '"Man,New,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"Men will confess to treason, murder, arson, false teeth, or a wig. How many of them will own up to a lack of humor?"', '"Men,Humor,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'That is the consolation of a little mind; you have the fun of changing it without impeding the progress of mankind.', '"Progress,Mind,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"The New York playgoer is a child of nature, and he has an honest and wholesome regard of whatever is atrocious in art."', '"Nature,Art,New"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'Persecution was at least a sign of personal interest. Tolerance is composed of nine parts of apathy to one of brotherly love.', '"Love,Tolerance,Personal"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"Talk ought always to run obliquely, not nose to nose with no chance of mental escape."', '"Chance,Escape,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"Clever people seem not to feel the natural pleasure of bewilderment, and are always answering questions when the chief relish of a life is to go on asking them."', '"Life,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'I have found some of the best reasons I ever had for remaining at the bottom simply by looking at the men at the top.', '"Best,Men,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'We always carry out by committee anything in which any one of us alone would be too reasonable to persist.', '"Alone,Always,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'Many people lose their tempers merely from seeing you keep yours.', '"Lose,People,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', 'One learns little more about a man from the feats of his literary memory than from the feats of his alimentary canal.', '"Man,Memory,More"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"If a large city can, after intense intellectual efforts, choose for its mayor a man who merely will not steal from it, we consider it a triumph of the suffrage."', '"Man,City,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe41', '"Politics is a place of humble hopes and strangely modest requirements, where all are good who are not criminal and all are wise who are not ridiculously otherwise."', '"Politics,Good,Wise"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe42', '"A heart is not judged by how much you love, but by how much you are loved by others."', '"Love,Valentines Day,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe42', 'It\'s my fault in many cases because I don\'t initiate the contact to talk with a lot of other musicians.', '"Talk,Fault,Initiate"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe42', 'I\'m eternally grateful to the penal system in California for saving my life.', '"Life,My Life,Grateful"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe42', '"Art led the way for me to recover. He got out of prison before me and started traveling all over the world before I did. He showed me by example that it could be done, and I\'ll always love him for that."', '"Love,Art,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe43', 'Strategy is buying a bottle of fine wine when you take a lady out for dinner. Tactics is getting her to drink it.', '"Dinner,Lady,Strategy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe43', '"Wit is a weapon. Jokes are a masculine way of inflicting superiority. But humor is the pursuit of a gentle grin, usually in solitude."', '"Humor,Solitude,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe44', 'Pushing production out of America to nations without our environmental standards increases global environmental risks.', '"Environmental,Risks,America"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe44', 'I firmly believe that we can have a healthy environment and a sustainable timber industry.', '"Environmental,Believe,Environment"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe44', 'Alaska has great potential for new oil and gas development.', '"Great,New,Development"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe44', 'One of Alaska\'s strengths is our pioneer role in environmentally sensitive development.', '"Development,Alaska,Sensitive"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', '"Freedom of speech, freedom of the press, and freedom of religion all have a double aspect - freedom of thought and freedom of action."', '"Freedom,Religion,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'Religious freedom is too sacred a right to be restricted or prohibited in any degree without convincing proof that a legitimate interest of the state is in grave danger.', '"Freedom,Degree,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'We would be false to our trust if we allowed the time it takes to give effect to constitutional rights to be used as the very reason for taking away those rights.', '"Trust,Time,Reason"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'I believe that nothing enjoys a higher estate in our society than the right given by the First and Fourteenth Amendments freely to practice and proclaim one\'s religious convictions.', '"Society,Believe,Practice"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'There was a time when the contractual relationship between the employer and the employee was supposed to be none of the public\'s business. That time has passed.', '"Business,Time,Relationship"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', '"It can feel like an invasion of privacy, involving an employer in a personal matter."', '"Feel,Privacy,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'The economy in the Valley will need to grow if students want to come back and work with their specialized degrees. We need to develop more to create more opportunities.', '"Work,Grow,Valley"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe45', 'The number one reason I write is to come to schools and see my readers. I would do it for free.', '"Free,See,Reason"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe46', '"The People have a right to the Truth as they have a right to life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness."', '"Life,Happiness,Truth"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe46', '"Truth is a thing immortal and perpetual, and it gives to us a beauty that fades not away in time."', '"Beauty,Truth,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe46', 'No art that is not in the end understood by the People can live or ever did live a single generation.', '"Art,Generation,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe46', 'The function of the novelist... is to comment upon life as he sees it.', '"Life,He,Comment"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'There\'s just some magic in truth and honesty and openness.', '"Truth,Honesty,Magic"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"As long as your intentions are solid and about growth and progression and being productive and not being idle, then you\'re doing good in my book."', '"Good,Growth,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'You just do what you can and you have as much fun as possible.', '"Fun,Possible,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I think we all change each other\'s paths. I don\'t know which law idea that is in physics, but I don\'t think any of us can live without affecting one another."', '"Change,Law,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'The Internet made fame wack and anonymity cool.', '"Cool,Internet,Fame"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"How we experience memory sometimes, it\'s not linear. We\'re not telling the stories to ourselves. We know the story; we\'re just seeing it in flashes overlaid."', '"Experience,Memory,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I believe that I\'m one of the best in the world at what I do, and that\'s all I\'ve ever wanted to be."', '"Best,Believe,World"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'You can\'t think; you just gotta do things.', '"Things,Think,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I don\'t have any secrets I need kept any more.', '"Secrets,More,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Art\'s everything we hope life would be, a lot of times."', '"Life,Hope,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'The Internet is just another experiment showing us more sides of us.', '"Internet,More,Experiment"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Obviously, the cinematography of films is art, just as a still shot can be art. If I\'m watching a Wes Anderson movie, the colour palettes alone, and the way they\'re painted, could be art. With music, you\'re a little bit limited, of course, because it\'s only audio."', '"Alone,Art,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"In art, at a certain level, there is no \'better than.\' It\'s just about trying to operate for yourself on the most supreme level, artistically, that you can and hoping that people get it. Trusting that, just because of the way people are built and how interconnected we are, greatness will translate and symmetry will be recognised."', '"Art,Yourself,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I don\'t intend to stop making music.', '"Music,Stop,Making"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I\'m about being the best.', '"Best,Being The Best,About"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'My music definitely comes from a place of experience. Everything connects to a truth.', '"Truth,Experience,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"My grandfather was smart and had a whole lot of pride. He didn\'t speak a terrible amount, but you could tell there was a ton on his mind - like a quiet acceptance of how life had turned out."', '"Life,Pride,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I wrote \'Channel Orange\' in two weeks. The end product wasn\'t always that gritty, real-life depiction of the real struggle that happened."', '"Struggle,Real,End"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"When I was growing up, there was nobody in my family - not even my mother - who I could look to and be like, \'I know you\'ve never said anything homophobic.\' So, you know, you worry about people in the business who you\'ve heard talk that way. Some of my heroes coming up talk recklessly like that."', '"Family,Business,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'A friend of mine jokes that I have a painstaking royalty complex. Like maybe I was a duke in a past life.', '"Life,Past,Royalty"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Boys do cry, but I don\'t think I shed a tear for a good chunk of my teenage years."', '"Good,Cry,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I had writer\'s block for almost a year.', '"Year,Almost,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Some people focus more on sonics. Some people focus more on story. I focus on both sonics and story, but music sometimes, just music itself, can turn into more of a maths problem. I guess everything in life is a math problem, but it can be more about an empirical route to getting the symmetry that you want, and this vibe, sonically."', '"Life,Music,Focus"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I play piano every day. I enjoy that.', '"Day,Every Day,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"It\'s about the stories. If I write 14 stories that I love, then the next step is to get the environment of music around it to best envelop the story, and all kinds of sonic goodness - sonic goodies."', '"Love,Best,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I\'m big on what\'s in good taste.', '"Good,Big,Taste"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Sometimes, I want to talk on a song and be angry, because I am angry. Then there\'s always a part of me that remembers that this record lives past my being angry, and so do I really want to be angry about that? Is that feeling going to have longevity?"', '"Angry,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I enjoy being involved in making the artwork for albums and stupid stuff like that.', '"Stupid,Enjoy,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I never think about myself as an artist working in this time. I think about it in macro.', '"Time,Myself,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'People are just afraid of things too much. Afraid of things that don\'t necessarily merit fear.', '"Fear,People,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I\'m extremely compassionate, loving, all of those warm fuzzy things, but the outer shell doesn\'t project that all the time."', '"Time,Project,Loving"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I\'ve always wanted to make a career in the arts, and I think that my only hope at doing that is to make it more about the work."', '"Work,Hope,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"This has always been my life and no one else\'s, and that\'s how it\'s always been since the day I came in it."', '"Life,My Life,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"The first four and a half years was me in the studio every day, writing songs for other people. I had jobs, too - eleven jobs. I worked at Kinko\'s, Fatburger, Subway - I was a sandwich artist - and I was a claims processor at Allstate Insurance."', '"Me,Day,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"It\'s more interesting for me to figure out how to be superior in areas where I\'m naive, where I\'m a novice."', '"Me,More,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I have no delusions about my likability in every scenario. I know that in order to get things done the way you want them, oftentimes your position will be unpopular."', '"Way,Done,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'It\'s cool to be recognised by your peers.', '"Cool,Your,Peers"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"We all know we have a finite period of time. I just feel if I\'m going to be alive, I want to be challenged - to be as immortal as possible. The path to that isn\'t an easy way, but it\'s a rewarding way."', '"Time,Path,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"As a writer, as a creator, I\'m giving you my experiences. But just take what I give you. You ain\'t got to pry beyond that."', '"Beyond,Creator,Giving"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I worked my face off.', '"Face,Off,Worked"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'Sometimes I\'m fascinated with how famous my work could be while I\'m not so famous.', '"Work,Famous,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I was a thug.', 'Thug', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I hope not to define myself by suffering.', '"Hope,Myself,Suffering"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Whenever I think about movies, I always look at that art process as having the best of a lot of worlds. Because if you watch a great film, you have a musical element to it, not just on the scoring, but in the way that the shots are edited - that has music and rhythm and time."', '"Best,Time,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"It started to weigh on me that I was responsible for the moves that had made me successful, but I wasn\'t reaping the lion\'s share of the profits, and that was problematic for me."', '"Me,Lion,Share"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I feel like I was writing as I was learning to talk. Writing was always a go-to form of communication. And I knew I could sing from being in tune with the radio.', '"Communication,Learning,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I grew up in New Orleans. I had just moved into my dorm at the University of New Orleans, and I was doing laundry, and my mom called me, like, \'We\'ve got to evacuate. There\'s a hurricane\'s coming.\'"', '"Mom,Me,New"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'Of course awards matter.', '"Matter,Awards,Course"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"All in all, I just don\'t trust journalists - and I don\'t think it\'s a good practice for me to trust journalists."', '"Trust,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'As a lifestyle you always being the focal point is innately unhealthy.', '"Lifestyle,Always,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I want to thank The Beatles for almost single-handedly getting me out of writer\'s block.', '"Me,Want,Beatles"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I\'ve written some great things. That\'s a gift, but there\'s consequences. Yeah, you get this great work, but you suffer. You really, really suffer."', '"Work,Great,Gift"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'We were poor. But my mom never accepted that. She worked hard to become a residential contractor - got her master\'s with honors at the University of New Orleans. I used to go to every class with her. Her father was my paternal figure.', '"Mom,Father,New"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I booked my first studio at like 12 or 13. Somewhere in that season of my life, singing along with the radio became me wanting to be on radio, you know. And writing Langston Hughes replica poems became me wanting to write like Stevie Wonder."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I might just write a novel next. I don\'t know!', '"Know,Next,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I won\'t touch on risky, because that\'s subjective. People are just afraid of things too much. Afraid of things that don\'t necessarily merit fear."', '"Fear,People,Touch"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I enjoy singing my songs in front of people. I enjoy being involved in making the artwork for albums and stupid stuff like that.', '"Stupid,Singing,People"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I don\'t fear anybody... at all.', '"Fear,Anybody"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I enjoy singing my songs in front of people.', '"Singing,People,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I make pop culture.', '"Culture,Pop Culture,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'Some people focus more on sonics. Some people focus more on story. I focus on both sonics and story.', '"Focus,People,Story"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I booked my first studio at like 12 or 13. Somewhere in that season of my life, singing along with the radio became me wanting to be on radio, you know."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"In art, at a certain level, there is no \'better than.\' It\'s just about trying to operate for yourself on the most supreme level, artistically, that you can and hoping that people get it."', '"Art,Yourself,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'The idea of recognising your strengths and using them in as versatile a way as you can is cool to me.', '"Cool,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I don\'t ever want to be caught up in a system of thinking I can do one thing \'cos that\'s just... that\'s just telling yourself a lie.', '"Thinking,Yourself,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I like the anonymity that directors can have about their films.', '"Like,About,Anonymity"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'Here\'s what I think about music and journalism: The most important thing is to just press play.', '"Music,Journalism,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I\'m in this business to be creative - I\'ll even diminish it and say to be a content provider.', '"Business,Say,Creative"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"In the studio, we adhere to a strict colour code. Developed over decades, the colour code consists of a finite and precise colour palate... The whole world as we experience it comes to us through the mystic realm of colour."', '"Experience,World,Colour"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I guess I\'m just inspired to tell stories.', '"Tell,Guess,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"You gotta make sure the listener is listening to you, so if you put it into a song, often times, if the song is striking enough, then you can really deliver the story most effectively while keeping the ear of the listener the whole time."', '"Time,Song,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Super-envious of the fact that Daft Punk can wear robot helmets and be one of the most famous bands in the world, while also understanding that will never be my situation."', '"Famous,World,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I\'ve gotten used to being Frank Ocean.', '"Ocean,Being,Frank"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"When I did have some success, it further emboldens you to be like, \'No, I\'m just going to write what I feel I should write.\'"', '"Success,Feel,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'The work is the work. The work is not me.', '"Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"Because I\'m not in a record deal, I don\'t have to operate in an album format."', '"Because,Deal,Album"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I can\'t usually stomach a project after I finish it, but for those days and weeks and months that it\'s new to me, I do listen to it, and it might change over time, but it\'s about function."', '"Change,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"The way I approach this thing, when I started to get my head screwed on straight and really trying to make something of myself as an artist, when I was 19 or 20, it became more about function for me. Like, what is this song doing to you? What is the function of this type of artform? What is it doing?"', '"Myself,Me,Song"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"When you write a song like \'Forrest Gump,\' the subject can\'t be androgynous. It requires an unnecessary amount of effort."', '"Effort,Song,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I can operate in half-a-song format.', '"I Can,Format,Operate"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'I respect Drake not only as a creative person but as a business mind as well. I think Drake\'s important.', '"Respect,Business,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', '"I need to know how many records I\'ve sold, how many album equivalents from streaming, which territories are playing my music more than others, because it helps me in conversations about where we\'re gonna be playing shows or where I might open a retail location, like a pop-up store or something."', '"Music,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'It\'s hard to articulate how I think about myself as a public figure.', '"Myself,Hard,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe48', 'It\'s not essential for me to have a big debut week; it\'s not essential for me to have big radio records.', '"Me,Big,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"A Jedi uses the Force for knowledge and defense, never for attack."', '"Knowledge,Never,Attack"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I have no idea what a British sensibility or a British sense of humor is. I have no concept of what that is. I have no concept of what American sensibility is. I was born in Great Britain, but I was only there for six months, and we moved to Belgium, where I grew up."', '"Humor,Great,Sense Of Humor"', '2023-05-29 12:01:00', '2023-05-29 12:01:00'),
	('398398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"Hope and Crosby made seven \'Road\' movies, starting in 1940 with \'Road to Singapore.\' The movies were always about Crosby and Hope fleeing America and finding Dorothy Lamour in some exotic location. Bob\'s character was cocky and cowardly; Bing\'s character was smooth and unruffled. They were great characters - lousy, lovable guys."', '"Hope,Great,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I bought a tape recorder and some stuff and went to Europe for three months when I was 18. The puppeteering was only there as a hobby. I wanted to be a journalist. When I was 19, and after I had spent about a year in college, Jim Henson asked me to come out and try puppeteering for awhile."', '"Me,Three,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', 'I\'m not an art director; I\'m just not. I\'ve always been somebody who has a sensibility that I hope is the same sensibility of others.', '"Hope,Art,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I was born in Hereford, England, in 1944. We moved when they had an opportunity to get a visa, about 1950. My dad always thought Europe was a bit too small for him. He wanted to see the United States... The typical immigrant story. He wanted a better life for his children, too. He always tried to get the visa, and it didn\'t come up."', '"Life,Dad,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I\'d like to read a book sometime. I\'ve never read a book before. That\'d be an adventure. I understand they have pages and everything. Yeah, I\'ve got to do that sometime."', '"Never,Everything,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I don\'t buy diamonds, I don\'t buy cars, but I enjoy travelling. I\'m not a very possessive person as far as things go."', '"Person,Diamonds,Possessive"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"Oakland Technical High School. Like any high-school experience, it was ambiguous. I was shy with girls; I had friends, but there were times I didn\'t feel I had the right friends. My grades were only so-so."', '"Experience,Feel,School"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"What I remember most about the \'Road\' movies is my enjoyment at watching the two characters sparring with each other. But more important than that was my feeling that Hope and Crosby were enjoying the sparring, too."', '"Hope,Movies,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I\'ve rewritten a lot of the scripts I\'ve done. \'Little Shop Of Horrors\' was a complete rewrite, but I didn\'t touch the dialogue. Essentially, I\'m a very good editor."', '"Good,Done,Touch"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"Always two there are, a master and an apprentice."', '"Always,Master,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I\'m not politically committed at all in the popular sense; that is, to any party. I\'m committed to whatever\'s best for the normal working person. I\'m not a great fan of politics."', '"Politics,Best,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"The more work I do, the more important it is to work with people I like - who are very talented."', '"Work,People,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', 'In order to be a star performer you have to have someone to play against.', '"Someone,Order,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', 'The biggest problems with movies are expectations.', '"Movies,Expectations,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I look back on my work and I think, \'Oh, why didn\'t I do that differently?\'"', '"Work,Look,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"Well, Hollywood isn\'t made up of individual studio heads anymore. It\'s made of corporations. And corporations are looking for the bottom line. They don\'t want to take chances. They want the money back for stockholders."', '"Money,Looking,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"\'The Stepford Wives\' was too big, and it was unsatisfying to do. Not that it was unsatisfying to do, but it was unsatisfying as a result because, as much as I loved parts of it, and I\'m really proud of so much of it, the entire movie wasn\'t what I wanted it to be. It\'s my own fault; I didn\'t follow my instincts."', '"Result,Proud,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I\'ve always wanted to do non-comedies. I\'ve always done dramas, comedies, music, and I always like to bop around and do different things."', '"Music,Done,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I never wanted to be a puppeteer. I stopped puppeteering when I was about 18. I puppeteered when I was eleven years old to 18 to make extra money to go to Europe, which I made half of and my parents gave me half."', '"Money,Me,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"The power of the \'Muppets,\' and the popularity of these characters, is so iconic in people\'s lives that I had to distance myself from publicly. Not privately... Privately, hell, I\'m with them for life, and I love these people. They\'re my second family."', '"Life,Love,Family"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"I wouldn\'t like to be that famous, I value my privacy. Mind you, Miss Piggy enjoys every moment of it. If it were not for me, she would spend all her time in the limelight."', '"Time,Famous,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', '"There\'s a few movies I wanted to do, and I didn\'t get to do them partly because they wanted me to be part of the horse and pony show, getting the money, and I\'m just not doing that. There\'s a few movies that people wanted me to do, but they were too safe."', '"Money,Movies,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe49', 'I love \'Time Bandits;\' it\'s great.', '"Love,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4a', 'It\'s important for us as Democrats to stick together.', '"Together,Important,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4a', 'My whole purpose really is to try to help working families to find better jobs and get better benefits and look out for the little guy.', '"Look,Purpose,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4b', 'It takes a tough man to make a tender chicken.', '"Man,Chicken,Tough"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4b', '"I never liked filming the ads, but they were so well received."', '"Never,Well,Filming"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4b', '"If you do this, you\'re going to have some heartaches from it. You\'re going to have people yelling at you or maybe screaming at you or criticizing you, but I think it\'s the best way to sell a superior chicken."', '"Best,Chicken,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4b', 'Baseball was a dream I gathered more splinters than hits.', '"More,Baseball,Dream"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"When people get their mind made up about something, then it\'s: \'Don\'t bother me with facts.\' They\'ve got their minds made up and dismiss you out of hand. Some people don\'t even give you a fair hearing."', '"Me,Mind,Facts"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"It\'s man\'s nature to abuse knowledge and power, be it in the realm of science, government, or Wall Street. Take God out of the picture, and you have real trouble."', '"Nature,God,Science"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"My earlier books, \'The Oath,\' \'This Present Darkness\' were pretty straight adventure. \'The Visitation\' is like a deeper book, more thought-provoking. It probes at character more."', '"Character,Darkness,Present"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"We have a God who loves us. We are in the palm of his hand. He doesn\'t leave us, and He doesn\'t forsake us."', '"God,Leave,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"My main goal is still for the books to minister in some way, to teach a spiritual truth, to enlighten people."', '"Truth,Spiritual,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I\'m given a lot of credit with opening the doors for Christian fiction. It was kind of a difficult field when I got into it... But I don\'t feel like a king.', '"King,Difficult,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I\'d like to write a series that, in an adventurous and fun way, teaches kids a way to discern between good and evil, to establish a foundation on moral absolutes."', '"Good,Fun,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I like doing thrillers.', '"Doing,Like,Thrillers"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I just feel the need as a writer to try something kind of deep and fulfilling.', '"Feel,Try,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I don\'t know what idea is going to hit me when.', '"Me,Know,Hit"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"There\'s nothing sacred about the book you\'ve written. The Bible says there\'s safety in a multitude of counselors. The movie is the movie, and the book is the book. They\'re different critters, and each must stand on their own merits."', '"Bible,Nothing,Stand"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'The Gospel can stand up to scrutiny.', '"Stand,Stand Up,Gospel"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I don\'t like to write boring books.', '"Boring,Like,Books"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I became very timid, very retreating. I wouldn\'t talk to anybody. I didn\'t look you in the eye. I just had that kind of personality as a kid that basically puts a target on you."', '"Personality,Look,Talk"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'The people that usually have the most trouble with my books are the ones that pick them apart from a theological point of view.', '"View,People,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"There are writers, and there are readers who want something more. They want to get at the grist of life."', '"Life,More,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I hear a lot of, \'I\'m a writer because of you.\' It\'s not a bad feeling, but it sneaks up on you. You don\'t ask for it."', '"Bad,Because,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"When you are writing for the Christian culture, there is a whole gamut of expectations."', '"Culture,Expectations,Writing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I don\'t watch television.', '"Television,Watch"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I\'m just a slow writer. I\'m picky and careful and fastidious.', '"Slow,Careful,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I wanted to write a novel where the meaning is in the story and characters and the subliminal, in the shades and nuances. It\'s exciting to develop that as a writer."', '"Story,Meaning,Shades"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"\'Illusion\' is a story of God\'s love and our hunger to find him when we\'re separated from him. If I can paint a picture of two people still in love after 40 years, that\'s a pretty good message."', '"Love,God,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I\'m trying to move a little more toward literary fiction while still retaining a popular feel.', '"Feel,Trying,More"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"When I first started out writing the \'Darkness\' books, there was, at least in my mind, a certain sort of rulebook we had to follow."', '"Mind,Darkness,Follow"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"A good book or movie or screenplay should be emotionally satisfying. When they\'re done, you want people to breathe a deep sigh and say, \'Wow.\'"', '"Good,People,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'I always want to be on the cutting edge.', '"Always,Edge,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', 'Kids are not going to sit and read a slow-paced book. Neither are adults.', '"Sit,Book,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"At the bottom of a Peretti novel is the biblical view of things, the Christian message. Whether you\'re a Christian or not, you\'re still going to have to deal with good versus evil."', '"Good,View,Evil"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"Some folks run from the doubt and go backward. You try for all the spiritual Band-Aids you can find... when actually, what you need to do is press forward, to accept those doubts and work through them."', '"Work,Spiritual,Accept"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"Evolution is the key to avoiding the whole issue of God. When you challenge evolution, you\'re basically challenging someone on a spiritual level."', '"God,Spiritual,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"There\'s a reason evolution is a hot-button issue. It\'s not just a matter of science, either. It\'s a matter of the big questions in life - why are we here, what is truth, where is our moral basis?"', '"Life,Science,Truth"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"If you\'re going to read a Peretti book, you\'re going to get a message. But the book is a pretty good read."', '"Good,Pretty,Book"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"The Lord God carries us throughout our lives just as a father carries his child. The Lord carried me, and He still is. He made you. He knows what you\'re good at. He knows what you can do and what you can become. Trust Him. Love Him. He\'ll always love you back."', '"Love,God,Trust"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"First of all, I was a good Christian kid. My mom and dad taught me never to fight. So I never fought. The other kids picked that up right away. They said, \'Oh, he\'s not going to try to do anything.\' They\'d push me, shove me, hit me. I\'d just stand there and take it."', '"Good,Mom,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"The logical outcome of evolution is that it makes monsters. We turn into monsters because evolution takes away everything that makes us human in the sense of our moral accountability, our moral absolutes, and our idea of being distinct from the animal kingdom."', '"Animal,Everything,Monsters"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"When I was a kid, I really got into monsters."', '"Monsters,Got,Kid"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"Moviemaking is just really neat, and I really like doing that. I\'d like to get into it more, but in terms of my role in all of this and in terms of the gift that God has given me, I had to come to the conclusion that my strength is as a storyteller, creating the story."', '"God,Strength,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"When you are making a movie, there are a zillion cooks in the kitchen, and you don\'t always get what you want to do. The story can always go in a different direction than what you would like. You compromise, and there is dealing and bickering."', '"Direction,Compromise,Kitchen"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"Just like all my novels, \'Illusion\' is a good way to observe where Frank Peretti was in his life when he wrote it."', '"Life,Good,Illusion"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I\'m a very methodical writer. Before computers, I used reams of paper and stacks of index cards."', '"Computers,Cards,Paper"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"Generally, my notes and outlines comprise more words than my novels. I suppose that\'s one reason I\'m a comparatively slow writer, something that has always bothered me given the fact that other authors can turn out a book every six months while I usually take about two years."', '"Me,Words,Slow"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4c', '"I try to write cinematically. Let me define what I mean by that. First of all, I try to write in a visual way so that the reader can watch a movie in their head. And it keeps moving. I try to structure the stories like a screenplay may be structured."', '"Me,Way,Moving"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4d', '"It used to be that we felt that when we went to a theater, a legitimate theater... that we were going to share an experience together. That when we walked away where there would be something to talk about in that movie that had some meaning and relevance in our lives. And I think that we have lost that."', '"Experience,Together,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4d', 'Movies are more than a commodity. Movies are to our civilization what dreams and ideals are to individual lives: They express the mystery and help define the nature of who we are and what we are becoming.', '"Dreams,Nature,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4d', '"There\'s no question that the \'70s themselves were really wide open. There was just so much being done at that time. Every year, the major studios were commissioning things that they would never touch today or even thought of touching in the 1950s."', '"Time,Today,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4d', '"Even a very brief tape-delay introduces a form of censorship into the broadcast - not direct governmental control, but it means that a network representative is in effect guessing at what a government might tolerate, which can be even worse."', '"Government,Control,Censorship"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4d', 'A \'live\' show is either alive or not. Free speech is free or it is not. Viewers are free to use their remote or TiVo. Parents are responsible or they are not.', '"Free,Parents,Alive"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"Fathering makes a man, whatever his standing in the eyes of the world, feel strong and good and important, just as he makes his child feel loved and valued."', '"Good,Eyes,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"Men who have been raised violently have every reason to believe it is appropriate for them to control others through violence; they feel no compunction over being violent to women, children, and one another."', '"Women,Men,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"No one, however powerful and successful, can function as an adult if his parents are not satisfied with him."', '"Parents,Satisfied,Adult"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"We know how powerful our mother was when we were little, but is our wife that powerful to us now? Must we relive our great deed of escape from Mama with every other woman in our life?"', '"Life,Great,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', 'A boy is not free to find a partner of his own as long as he must be the partner to his mother.', '"Long,Free,Partner"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"A man doesn\'t have to have all the answers; children will teach him how to parent them, and in the process will teach him everything he needs to know about life."', '"Life,Man,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"Each generation\'s job is to question what parents accept on faith, to explore possibilities, and adapt the last generation\'s system of values for a new age."', '"Faith,Age,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"Parents can make us distrust ourselves. To them, we seem always to be works-in-progress."', '"Parents,Always,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4e', '"Why do otherwise sane, competent, strong men, men who can wrestle bears or raid corporations, shrink away in horror at the thought of washing a dish or changing a diaper?"', '"Men,Why,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', 'I had an agenda. It was a very smooth transition.', '"Transition,Smooth,Agenda"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', 'Gutenberg and Richter were very great men.', '"Men,Great,Great Men"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', 'For my own personal growth I had to set out on my own.', '"Growth,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', '"When the first computers started to come in, we tried to digitalize the seismological equipment."', '"Computers,Tried,First"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', 'It\'s a difficult question of relations between people.', '"Difficult,People,Question"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', '"My attitude toward graduate students was different, I must say. I used graduate students as colleagues: I gave them the best problems to work on, and I encouraged them."', '"Attitude,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe4f', '"You travel across the country, you visit departments, you give talks, you talk about the work at your laboratory - what\'s going on, what the opportunities are there - you talk about your own research."', '"Work,Travel,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', 'Don\'t go public before you can be public.', '"Go,Before,Public"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', '"We don\'t have sales trading, brokerage, capital lending - any of those kinds of things that got some of the Wall Street firms a little bit in trouble."', '"Street,Trouble,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', '"We have a network of contacts, where there are very few boards where we can\'t reach out to the CEO or key board members."', '"Reach,Key,CEO"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', 'LinkedIn is the Netscape of its era.', '"Era,LinkedIn,Netscape"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', 'Twitter has a several-hour advantage in getting information.', '"Information,Twitter,Advantage"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', 'I don\'t follow any particular periodical anymore. I use Twitter as my customized news feed.', '"News,Follow,Use"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', '"I was fortunate that I came out to the Valley in 1979, when I came out to go to Stanford Business School, and my very first assignment as a teaching assistant for an investments professor was to - he told me go down to this computer company in Cupertino called Apple."', '"Business,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', '"I thought I was kind of a hotshot because I had had two years of work experience at Morgan Stanley, and I was about to get my Stanford M.B.A."', '"Work,Experience,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', '"When we took Netscape public, if people wanted to invest in the web, that was the only stock that they could do it by investing in. So Netscape\'s market value was higher than it probably otherwise would have been if there were lots of other ways to play that theme."', '"Value,People,Theme"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe50', 'Respect public investors and treat them as partners and important constituents.', '"Respect,Treat,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe51', '"Let\'s nail it down, let\'s get it right."', '"Down,Right,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe51', 'I think your program has to reflect what your basic feelings are. I\'ll plead guilty to that.', '"Feelings,Guilty,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"History is cyclical, and it would be foolhardy to assume that the culture wars will never return."', '"History,Culture,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"Looking back at my high school years, I\'m struck by how slowly history can move."', '"History,Looking Back,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"\'Up in the Air\' may be a glossy production sprinkled with laughter and sex, but it captures the distinctive topography of our Great Recession as vividly as a far more dour Hollywood product of 70 years ago, \'The Grapes of Wrath,\' did the vastly different landscape of the Great Depression."', '"Great,Sex,Laughter"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"One of the most persistent cultural tics of the early 21st century is Americans\' reluctance to absorb, let alone prepare for, bad news."', '"Alone,News,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"When something really comes from the soul, I think it has a truth that you cannot find in politics."', '"Politics,Truth,Soul"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', 'Americans have less and less patience for the intrusive and divisive moral scolds who thrived in the bubbles of the Clinton and Bush years.', '"Patience,Moral,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"It is kind of tedious after a while, to parse politicians doing the same thing over and over again. The facts change from week to week, but the sort of masquerade doesn\'t."', '"Change,Facts,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"In the bubble decade, making money as an end in itself boomed as a calling among students at elite universities like Harvard, siphoning off gifted undergraduates who might otherwise have been scientists, teachers, doctors, entrepreneurs, artists or inventors."', '"Money,Making Money,End"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', 'There have been at least three other cases in which federal agencies have succeeded in placing fake news reports on television during the Bush presidency. It was a really good tour. It seemed maybe about a week too long.', '"Good,Long,News"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"No one is better placed or more philosophically suited than Obama to construct the new counter narrative as we go forward in our new New Deal. But many masters of the old universe, including quite possibly his chief economic adviser, can\'t recognize that the world has changed or should change."', '"Change,World,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"As America knows, Obama turned down the lucrative career path guaranteed to the first African-American president of The Harvard Law Review to pursue the missions of service and teaching instead. The potential rewards for our country, now that that early choice has led him into the White House, are enormous."', '"Path,Service,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', 'Nationalization would likely mean wiping out the big banks\' managements and shareholders. It\'s because that reckoning has mostly been avoided so far that those bankers may be the Americans in the greatest denial of all.', '"Big,Mean,Far"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"Unless and until Barack Obama addresses the full depth of Americans\' anger with his full arsenal of policy smarts and political gifts, his presidency and, worse, our economy will be paralyzed."', '"Anger,Political,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"While F.D.R. once told Americans that we have nothing to fear but fear itself, Mr. Ashcroft is delighted to play the part of Fear Itself, an assignment in which he lets his imagination run riot."', '"Fear,Imagination,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"After 9/11, we realized that all these silly culture wars, and arguing about rock lyrics... who cares? You know, we, for some reason, remembered what our real problems are."', '"Culture,Problems,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"In that sense, when a Bush or a Gore, or whomever, goes on David Letterman, that\'s the news, too."', '"News,Sense,David"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"I grew up in Washington, D.C. But also loving the theater."', '"Loving,Up,Washington"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"I\'m always struck by the kids who turn up in New York and LA, and places in between. Chicago. Wanting to do theater, wanting to do independent film. Wanting to break into television or radio."', '"New,Independent,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"For a man who purports to have learned of media ethics only this month, Mr. Williams has spent an undue amount of time appearing as a media ethicist on both CNN and the cable news networks of NBC."', '"Time,Man,Ethics"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', 'Of course most Americans don\'t know how A.I.G. brought the world\'s financial system to near-ruin or what credit-default swaps are. They may not even know what A.I.G. stands for. But Americans do make the connection between their fears about their own jobs and their broad understanding of the A.I.G. debacle.', '"World,Connection,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"Someday we\'ll learn the whole story of why George W. Bush brushed off that intelligence briefing of Aug. 6, 2001, \'Bin Laden Determined to Strike in U.S.\' But surely a big distraction was the major speech he was readying for delivery on Aug. 9, his first prime-time address to the nation."', '"Intelligence,Delivery,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"The cruel ambush of 9/11 supposedly \'changed everything,\' slapping us back to reality. Yet we are constantly shocked, shocked by the foreseeable."', '"Reality,Back,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"Nationalization, unmentionable only yesterday, has entered common usage not least because an even scarier word - depression - is next on America\'s list to avoid."', '"America,Yesterday,Depression"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"Feckless as it was for Bush to ask Americans to go shopping after 9/11, we all too enthusiastically followed his lead, whether we were wealthy, working-class or in between. We spent a decade feasting on easy money, don\'t-pay-as-you-go consumerism and a metastasizing celebrity culture."', '"Money,Culture,Shopping"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"My particular historical vantage point is a product of my upbringing as that odd duck, a native Washingtonian whose parents were not in government. The first presidential transition of my sentient lifetime, Kennedy\'s, I remember vividly."', '"Government,Duck,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '"One would like to say in the aftermath of the 2008 election that everyone lived happily ever after. But the American drama, especially when it involves race, is always more complicated than that."', '"Drama,Election,American"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe52', '\'Up in the Air\' is not a political movie. It won\'t be mistaken for either a Michael Moore or Any Rand polemic on capitalism.', '"Political,Capitalism,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe53', '"I think I won\'t do for your business at all, but personally I have no fight with you. You can go on and save all the critics you can, but don\'t send them to me."', '"Business,Fight,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe53', '"I had my share of critics, and I wash my hands of the whole lot."', '"Hands,Critics,Share"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe53', 'May you live to see the green grass growing over your grave.', '"Green,Grass,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I always had much respect for Rudi Voller.', '"Respect,Always,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I see a lot of fouls on Messi, and he\'s not the type to overreact."', '"See,I See,He"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Manchester United is a world-famous club, and yet if you say, \'Manchester United,\' then immediately you think of Sir Alex Ferguson. To have achieved so much and have so much importance at such a big club is extremely rare."', '"Big,Sir,Rare"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Without a doubt, it is easier to produce a defensive soccer team, because it does not need you to have talent for it but simply to be well organised."', '"Talent,Doubt,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'The differences between the top teams in Euro 2000 are so minimal that I think you have to be very clever in defence and stop your opponents getting opportunities.', '"Differences,Clever,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"At Barcelona, I was exposed to talent. You had Ronaldinho, who was a marvel to watch. Deco is skilful and talented. Then there are players like Xavi, a good and hardworking man who gave his all. Iniesta is another. Then the name of Messi will come up in that list."', '"Good,Man,Talent"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Someone said that my coaching is a combination of Milan\'s defensive discipline and the Dutch propensity for attacking football, and I think that is a fair description."', '"Football,Discipline,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"He\'s an incredible person. Messi is not simply a uniquely talented footballer. He\'s also strong mentally, very bright, and exceptionally dedicated to his job. Personally speaking, I enjoy watching him play, and I\'m deeply proud of him and what he has achieved. Quite simply, he\'s the best."', '"Best,Person,Watching"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'The level of English teams is high.', '"High,Level,English"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Generally speaking, I think that Frank Lampard is one of the best players in international football."', '"Best,Football,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Most of the clubs who have had success against Barcelona have relied on a highly organised and disciplined defence.', '"Success,Defence,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"He was always brilliant, but when Pep Guardiola started to use him as a \'false\' No. 9, he got even better. It\'s impossible to be more of a footballer than Messi."', '"Impossible,Better,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'It is very tough to beat an English team. The type of football they play is only in the Premier League. They defend as though their lives depend on it. And they are very successful.', '"Football,Tough,Beat"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"The situation with Anders Frisk is clear: he was threatened by the supporters of Chelsea, and he retired because he was in fear. This is serious."', '"Fear,Situation,Serious"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"We have to remember, Mourinho worked at Barcelona. He has good memories of Barcelona. The club did well when he was here."', '"Good,Memories,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"With every coach you work with, you learn something. Then, at the end of your career, when you become a trainer, you take something from every coach that you think is useful for you."', '"Work,End,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"There are coaches with habits you don\'t like, and you tell yourself, \'I don\'t want to be like that.\' But there\'s no one way to success."', '"Success,Yourself,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"The Dutch public always wants to see a team that is trying to be dominant, trying to play attractive football, and after that, hopefully, a team that is winning."', '"Football,Winning,See"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"In the end, every coach wants the same - that\'s to win."', '"Win,End,In The End"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Mourinho is very intelligent; he knows what he\'s doing. He has the right to act like he wants to act, and he\'s very successful with it, so who am I to criticise him?"', '"Doing,Intelligent,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"We can be confident about our qualities, but the qualities need something to come out."', '"Need,Something,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"You always need to have the highest respect for your opponents. If you see them fighting, you know you have to give something extra."', '"Respect,Fighting,See"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'It\'s always the losers who are complaining about a result.', '"Result,Always,Complaining"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I have a great deal of respect for Sir Alex Ferguson. He has done a great job. Without any doubt, he is one of the best and most influential around. He is the embodiment of football."', '"Best,Respect,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I try to stay in the moment.', '"Moment,Try,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"When it\'s a clash between two big teams, you know your players will concentrate."', '"Will,Know,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'How can you judge a man until you come face to face?', '"Man,Face,Judge"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'My aim is to get the team to work hard and stay strong together.', '"Work,Together,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"There is a part of football I would describe as \'serious\' and one part I would describe as more \'playful,\' i.e. more technical."', '"Football,Serious,Playful"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'The goal is always to win.', '"Win,Always,Goal"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I am completely uninterested in playing beautiful football if the team doesn\'t win.', '"Beautiful,Football,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I made Edgar Davids vice-captain. Nothing to do with colour, just because he was playing excellently and because he lives like an athlete."', '"Nothing,Just Because,Colour"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"After your career, you go to matches, and you see so many unnecessary goals because a person is just looking where the ball is and not his opponent. Well, a ball alone has never scored a goal."', '"Alone,Goals,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"As a young centre-back at Ajax, I played with Wim Jansen, and of course you learn a huge amount. I made some mistakes, because we Dutchmen want to solve situations by playing football. So we look at the ball, try to judge where it will come."', '"Football,Look,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"One thing was crystal clear to me: if you\'re centre-back, you first of all have to perform your task."', '"Me,Crystal,Task"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"We win together, and we lose together."', '"Together,Lose,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Losing against rivals is always a blow to the morale.', '"Losing,Always,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"When a parent has two children, it is difficult to pick one favourite."', '"Children,Difficult,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"It would not be honest if I did a review, because I\'ve worked with Leo Messi, whom I consider the best player I\'ve seen. I cannot comment or compare with Cristiano Ronaldo because I have not worked with him. That is not to say that I do not have as much respect for Cristiano as a footballer."', '"Best,Respect,Review"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Players are sometimes sad, sometimes happy during their sporting career."', '"Sad,Sometimes,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"If you want to come out of a sad moment, you have to work really hard."', '"Work,Sad,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"From the moment Messi was introduced, we all knew he was a unique talent. I remember Deco and Ronaldinho immediately realised how special he was, and they took him under their wing."', '"Moment,Talent,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I have no desire to be 60 years old and standing on the side of the pitch.', '"Desire,Old,Standing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I\'m grateful for everything I have achieved in football, but now I\'d rather do other things, go and watch games and enjoy discussing them afterwards."', '"Football,Grateful,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"As a player, you are more concerned with the moments when you have possession of the ball or are about to receive the ball. You are watching your team-mates and trying to decide what the possibilities are."', '"Watching,Trying,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"When you are a coach, you are watching how the team is positioning itself on the field - if your team is in possession of the ball, you are already anticipating what could happen if you lose the ball."', '"Lose,Watching,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I understand very well that if you are a national coach, you want to use all the opportunities that you have to meet up with your team."', '"Understand,Meet,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"The evolution of football has seen a reduction in the space between the teams. It is therefore important for the modern footballer to react and be quicker than in the past, because there is more happening in the restricted space."', '"Space,Football,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"No person is the same, and so you can\'t treat each player identically."', '"Treat,Person,Same"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Being a manager is kneading people.', '"People,Being,Manager"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I\'m not a guy who believes in revenge.', '"Revenge,Guy,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Ronaldinho is very happy at Barcelona.', '"Happy,Barcelona,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'It is always a shame when players are injured.', '"Always,Shame,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Pavarotti is not judged on how he sings in the shower. People wait until he gets on stage.', '"Wait,People,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'It\'s not for nothing that they say it\'s easier to get to the top than to stay at the top.', '"Nothing,They Say,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"It\'s normal that if you are working with a lot of people, then you have a lot of different mentalities and characters. You have the serious guy, and you have the one who is always complaining and the one who is always talking. Everyone is different."', '"People,Serious,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I can work with a lot of different mentalities.', '"Work,I Can,Different"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Every manager feels a responsibility to his board of directors and the public and the players.', '"Responsibility,Players,Public"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'You see a lot of managers who are working and yet are already talking about other countries and other teams. But that\'s not for me.', '"Me,See,Talking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'All the big clubs set their goals. We have to do that because it is necessary to explain to the fans. But this does not mean I am thinking only of the final results. The work you are doing every day with the team is often more important.', '"Work,Thinking,Goals"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'The national team means you have the nation behind it.', '"Nation,Behind,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'You have to score one goal more than your opponents. That\'s the most important thing.', '"Important,Your,More"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Dennis is something special. We are talking a lot about exciting football, and Dennis Bergkamp, I think, started with attractive football a long time ago. He was one of these players. A lot of the things he did as a football player you can compare to art."', '"Time,Art,Football"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"If someone is quite tall, the people will sing songs about his height. We don\'t have to overreact. You just have to do your job."', '"People,Will,Tall"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I think that every manager who starts work with a team has the best expectations and is giving all he\'s got to improve immediately.', '"Work,Best,Expectations"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"A team like Barcelona always has targets, and that\'s quite normal."', '"Always,Normal,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Before we talk about stylish performance, we need to think about winning. That\'s the most important thing."', '"Winning,Important,Performance"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Mourinho is a great coach, and I respect the way he works."', '"Respect,Great,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Everyone has his own form, and I never had any problems with Mourinho."', '"Problems,Never,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Mourinho follows his personality - staying close to his own way - he chooses that, and he has been very successful with it. I can only have respect for that."', '"Respect,Personality,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Short-termism is no good: plans must be carried through to the end.', '"Good,End,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"I had a lot of success, of course, but whatever was achieved was due to a group effort on the part of all the players."', '"Success,Effort,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'It\'s my belief that Barcelona are successful because they have a number of youth teams alongside the first team. They are where it begins.', '"Youth,Belief,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Success is built on organisation, determination, and experience, not to mention following the regulations, so of course it\'s no easy matter."', '"Success,Experience,Determination"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'Africa has produced some good players.', '"Good,Africa,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', '"Ronaldinho is another special player, probably amongst the most talented players I have worked with. At Barcelona, he was outstanding."', '"Special,Players,He"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe54', 'I was once in charge of the Dutch team - and then I was introduced to club football!', '"Football,Club,Once"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe55', 'A conservative is a liberal who got mugged the night before.', '"Night,Conservative,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe55', '"The streets are safe in Philadelphia, it\'s only the people that make them unsafe."', '"People,Safe,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"All in all, I wouldn\'t call it a bad outing. It was a short outing."', '"Outing,Bad,Short"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'Close don\'t count in baseball. Close only counts in horseshoes and grenades.', '"Baseball,Only,Close"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"I always tried to do the best. I knew I couldn\'t always be the best, but I tried to be."', '"Best,Always,Tried"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'It\'s nice to come into a town and be referred to as the manager of the Cleveland Indians instead of as the first black manager.', '"Black,Nice,First"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"During the years I was still playing, I would go to Puerto Rico in the winter and manage. When the day came, I had the experience without having to go to the minor leagues for four or five years and then wait for an opportunity. Still, there\'s a double standard. Some whites, like Pete Rose, Joe Torre and Ted Williams, never had to go to the minors."', '"Experience,Opportunity,Wait"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"People come out to see the players. When do you see a manager anyway? When he\'s out on the field arguing with the umpires, making a fool of himself and you know you can\'t win, and when he brings out the line-up card."', '"Fool,People,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"I haven\'t seen a player in this game, as long as I\'ve been in it, that can\'t be pitched to... Barry is an outstanding ballplayer. I respect him an awful lot. I also have confidence in my pitchers that they can pitch to Barry Bonds and get him out."', '"Respect,Confidence,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"If the guys on the bench were as good as the guys you have out there, they\'d be out there in first place."', '"Good,Place,Bench"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"Pitchers did me a favor when they knocked me down. It made me more determined. I wouldn\'t let that pitcher get me out. They say you can\'t hit if you\'re on your back, but I didn\'t hit on my back. I got up."', '"Me,Back,They Say"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"The fan is the one who suffers. He cheers a guy to a .350 season then watches that player sign with another team. When you destroy fan loyalties, you destroy everything."', '"Everything,Watches,Fan"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"I know a lot of people on the field - players, coaches, managers - are glad that I\'m gone."', '"People,Know,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"At least when it\'s in French, I won\'t know what the heck they\'re saying."', '"Know,Saying,Least"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"No. 1, these guys out here on this field. They keep my energy level up. They try hard, they don\'t complain about things - and I\'d just like to be with them when things are good, and hopefully we can win a pennant together."', '"Good,Together,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'Managers don\'t have as much leverage as they used to have. We can\'t really be the boss.', '"Boss,Leverage,Much"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"No, I don\'t think my presence will cause an increase in black attendance at Cleveland."', '"Black,Will,Presence"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"If he can hit, he can hit. I don\'t care if he came from Class Z league."', '"Care,dont Care,He"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"But I\'m not going to walk Barry Bonds, like some teams do, in the first inning with nobody on."', '"Walk,Nobody,First"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'You have to have a short memory as a closer.', '"Memory,Short,Closer"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"I just didn\'t have anything to say, so I said nothing."', '"Nothing,Anything,Said"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"The way we\'re going... if I called up another pitcher, he\'d just hang up the phone on me."', '"Me,Way,Phone"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'Al Campanis made people finally understand what goes on behind closed doors - that there is racism in baseball.', '"People,Doors,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"I\'ve never seen baseball advertise for a job, and I\'ve never heard of whites applying for a job. I mean, there\'s an old boy network, and it\'s lily white."', '"White,Never,Boy"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"As a black, you find you have to be two or three times better than a white even to play. And when it comes to front-office jobs, management believes you\'ll never be as good."', '"Good,Black,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', '"It was a breaking period for black people coming into baseball, and how many followed depended on Jackie\'s conduct. But that\'s not the case now. What and how I do doesn\'t mean nearly as much as what and how Jackie did."', '"Black,People,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'I wanted to show Baltimore that they were getting a good ballplayer.', '"Good,Show,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe56', 'I played with some outstanding players.', '"Players,Some,Outstanding"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe57', '"Never apologize, mister. It\'s a sign of weakness."', '"Never,Weakness,Apologize"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe57', 'The army is always the same. The sun and the moon change. The army knows no seasons.', '"Change,Moon,Sun"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe58', '"I have three degrees in history and only one in law, but since I came back to specialize in constitutional law where history is so essentially a part and an explanation of much that exists, the two disciplines blended very well."', '"History,Law,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe58', 'Oxford also taught me something else - it taught me scepticism.', '"Me,Something,Oxford"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe58', 'I was brought in touch with developing post World War I ideas in Europe.', '"War,World,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe58', 'I think it\'s perhaps fair to say we\'ve been one of the most influential Royal Commissions this country ever had and there\'s nothing we have said that isn\'t relevant to the present situation.', '"Situation,Country,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', '"The fight for justice against corruption is never easy. It never has been and never will be. It exacts a toll on our self, our families, our friends, and especially our children. In the end, I believe, as in my case, the price we pay is well worth holding on to our dignity."', '"Fight,Justice,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', 'I\'m retarded - I mean I\'m retired.', '"Mean,Retired"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', 'An honest cop still can\'t find a place to go and complain without fear of recrimination. The blue wall will always be there because the system supports it.', '"Fear,Blue,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', '"I had gone through a near-death experience, and that gives you an insight into how fleeting life is, and what\'s important."', '"Life,Experience,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', '"I used to think, \'How can I write my life story? I\'m still living it.\'"', '"Life,My Life,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', '"Today it is becoming harder to speak out, with the inception of the Patriot Act, the president has legislated free speech to be a crime."', '"Today,Free,Speak"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe59', '"My acting career began on the streets of New York. When I was a cop, I played many impressive roles, from derelict to a doctor, and my life often depended on my performance."', '"Life,Doctor,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'The weather is perfect. The gods are shining on us.', '"Weather,Perfect,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"Experience has taught me how important it is to just keep going, focusing on running fast and relaxed. Eventually it passes and the flow returns. It\'s part of racing."', '"Experience,Keep Going,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"To put it another way, Michael Jordan was a gym rat."', '"Way,Rat,Michael Jordan"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'Intervals and other types of speed work are essential to improve running speed.', '"Work,Speed,Types"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'Because running fast is more fun than running slow.', '"Fun,Fast,Slow"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"As I\'ve been able to once again gain the benefits of speed work, I\'m enjoying my running more and more."', '"Work,Speed,More"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'Hills are speedwork in disguise.', '"Disguise,Hills"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'You don\'t run 26 miles at five minutes a mile on good looks and a secret recipe.', '"Good,Secret,Miles"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"It is just called Continuing Legal Education. You can go to lectures, you can even listen to tapes on airplanes - they want you to stay current. So you do have to stay current to maintain your license even if you are not practicing."', '"Education,Legal,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"I think the secret of my light, quick, foot strike is related to the fact that I have fragile feet."', '"Light,Feet,Secret"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"The irony of that is, what makes it kind of ironic, is when you do become successful as a professional athlete in particular, a lot of the young children who are emulating these stars do have a different perspective."', '"Stars,Perspective,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"The potential elite runner must realize that hard means hard, easy means easy and they must patiently seek out what combinations work for them. They have to learn to be persistent and patient with their training and racing."', '"Work,Training,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"A good athlete always mentally replays a competition over and over, even in victory, to see what might be done to improve the performance the next time."', '"Time,Good,Competition"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"Again, racing for me was about energy management."', '"Me,Energy,Management"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'Being in school is the best place to be if you are an athlete because you can structure your own time.', '"Best,Time,School"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"For the novice runner, I\'d say to give yourself at least 2 months of consistently running several times a week at a conversational pace before deciding whether you want to stick with it. Consistency is the most important aspect of training at this point."', '"Consistency,Yourself,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'I admire runners older than I - they are now my heroes. I want to be like them as I grow older.', '"Grow,Admire,Heroes"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'I also held several masters running titles.', '"Titles,Running,Masters"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'I plan to be running as long as I can and have no plans to stop.', '"Long,I Can,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"I started in law school in \'71 and graduated in \'74. So I was training for the Olympics, running or averaging around 20 miles a day and going to law school full time."', '"Time,Training,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"I think he had a wake-up call. It\'s a different kind of race, and I think maybe he didn\'t take it quite as seriously as he might have, but you can bet he learned a lot of lessons."', '"Race,Seriously,Bet"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'I think it is that parents just don\'t kick their kids out the door as much as they used to. I think the demise of sandlot sports has had a lot to do with it.', '"Sports,Parents,Door"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'I was actually going to law school in 1972.', '"Law,School,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'In other words we have marketed our way into this health crisis.', '"Health,Words,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'It is not the time spent with the child at their activity that is going to produce the highest level athlete. It is in supporting the child in an organized activity - and Bill alluded to this - so the child can find what they truly like to do and let them go.', '"Time,Find,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'My goal is to break three hours in a marathon.', '"Three,Break,Marathon"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"Really, I think that going out and playing with your friends is kind of becoming a lost art, with the kids in the neighborhood."', '"Art,Lost,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"Right now, after having had back surgery, I am finally back to running again."', '"I Am,Back,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'Running with others can help get you out when you might otherwise blow it off.', '"Help,Others,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"So, in a way I was hedging and saying that if the Olympic stuff doesn\'t work out at least I can be a lawyer."', '"Work,Lawyer,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"The marathon is all about energy management. I had planned to run it like a track race with strategic surges to blow up my competitors by putting them into oxygen debt, so that is the way I prepared."', '"Energy,Way,Management"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'There\'s obviously some validity to it. But I think it also points out that you obviously can do it on your own because people have been doing it long before they had the stuff.', '"Long,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'What you did was live on very little. I think all of us that were competing - Bill is the same way - you don\'t need much to live.', '"Way,Live,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"When I am totally race fit, I don\'t worry about breathing or technique - they take care of themselves."', '"I Am,Care,Worry"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', 'When you are caring about your children perhaps you always have to remember at what point you can become over involved because of something you need rather than something the child needs.', '"Children,Caring,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5a', '"Yes, winning the gold medal was undoubtedly the biggest day of my career - mostly because I won the way I had prepared to run it. It was a totally satisfying experience."', '"Experience,Day,Winning"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5b', 'I started out years ago as a theater major and got disillusioned with it. It\'s a rough business.', '"Business,Rough,Years Ago"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5b', 'I\'m trying to treat it as a hobby. Making bread and butter as an actor is tough.', '"Treat,Tough,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'The best revenge is massive success.', '"Success,Best,Revenge"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'Cock your hat - angles are attitudes.', '"Attitude,Hat,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Basically, I\'m for anything that gets you through the night - be it prayer, tranquilizers or a bottle of Jack Daniels."', '"Prayer,Night,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'May you live to be 100 and may the last voice you hear be mine.', '"Live,Voice,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Alcohol may be man\'s worst enemy, but the bible says love your enemy."', '"Love,Man,Bible"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I would like to be remembered as a man who had a wonderful time living life, a man who had good friends, fine family - and I don\'t think I could ask for anything more than that, actually."', '"Life,Family,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"You gotta love livin\', baby, \'cause dyin\' is a pain in the ass."', '"Love,Pain,Baby"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"For my money, Tony Bennett is the best singer in the business. He excites me when I watch him. He moves me. He\'s the singer who gets across what the composer has in mind, and probably a little more."', '"Best,Business,Money"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I like intelligent women. When you go out, it shouldn\'t be a staring contest."', '"Women,Intelligent,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"A man doesn\'t know what happiness is until he\'s married. By then, it\'s too late."', '"Happiness,Man,Late"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'Dare to wear the foolish clown face.', '"Face,Dare,Clown"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Rock \'n Roll: The most brutal, ugly, desperate, vicious form of expression it has been my misfortune to hear."', '"Ugly,Rock,Expression"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'I\'m gonna live till I die.', '"Death,Die,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"You treat a lady like a dame, and a dame like a lady."', '"Treat,Lady,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'I\'m for whatever gets you through the night.', '"Funny,Night,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I\'m supposed to have a Ph.D. on the subject of women. But the truth is I\'ve flunked more often than not. I\'m very fond of women; I admire them. But, like all men, I don\'t understand them."', '"Truth,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'Hell hath no fury like a hustler with a literary agent.', '"Hell,Hustler,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I\'m not one of those complicated, mixed-up cats. I\'m not looking for the secret to life... I just go on from day to day, taking what comes."', '"Life,Day,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"What I do with my life is of my own doing. I live it the best way I can. I\'ve been criticized on many, many occasions, because of - acquaintances, and what have you."', '"Life,Best,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"People often remark that I\'m pretty lucky. Luck is only important in so far as getting the chance to sell yourself at the right moment. After that, you\'ve got to have talent and know how to use it."', '"Chance,Moment,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Whatever else has been said about me personally is unimportant. When I sing, I believe. I\'m honest."', '"Me,Believe,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I believe that God knows what each of us wants and needs. It\'s not necessary for us to make it to church on Sunday to reach Him. You can find Him anyplace. And if that sounds heretical, my source is pretty good: Matthew, Five to Seven, The Sermon on the Mount."', '"God,Good,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I\'m like Albert Schweitzer and Bertrand Russell and Albert Einstein in that I have a respect for life - in any form. I believe in nature, in the birds, the sea, the sky, in everything I can see or that there is real evidence for. If these things are what you mean by God, then I believe in God."', '"Life,Nature,God"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Oh, I just wish someone would try to hurt you so I could kill them for you."', '"Wish,Someone,Hurt"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Don\'t get even, get mad."', '"Mad,Get,Even"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'I am a thing of beauty.', '"Beauty,I Am,Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"There are things about organized religion which I resent. Christ is revered as the Prince of Peace, but more blood has been shed in His name than any other figure in history. You show me one step forward in the name of religion, and I\'ll show you a hundred retrogressions."', '"History,Peace,Religion"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Nothing anybody\'s said or written about me ever bothers me, except when it does."', '"Me,Nothing,Said"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"My father had a piano that was a nickelodeon - put a nickel, and the roller would play."', '"Father,Play,Piano"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Our civilization, such as it is, was shaped by religion, and the men who aspire to public office anyplace in the free world must make obeisance to God or risk immediate opprobrium."', '"God,Men,Religion"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"I\'m trying to figure out, Chairman of what Board? People come up to me and seriously say: \'Well, what are you Chairman of?\' And I can\'t answer them."', '"Me,People,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"In Hoboken, when I was a kid, I lived in a plenty tough neighborhood."', '"Tough,Neighborhood,Lived"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', 'The martial music of every sideburned delinquent on the face of the earth.', '"Music,Face,Earth"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5c', '"Throughout my career, if I have done anything, I have paid attention to every note and every word I sing - if I respect the song. If I cannot project this to a listener, I fail."', '"Respect,Song,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I think the dirtiest word in the English language is retirement. When you do that, you get old and you get sick and you die."', '"Die,Language,Retirement"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'The recording companies are continuing to look at ways to buy short and sell long. So now they give recording deals to groups of people who we refer to as \'garage bands\' - they are amateurs who are bought for nothing and it\'s really a shame.', '"Look,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'It\'s OK if people say I sound like Frank Sinatra. I just don\'t want them to think I am Frank Sinatra.', '"I Am,People,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'When I was working at the Flamingo I took slides of people standing in front of the Flamingo with the highway behind them. Across the street you can see these tumbleweeds. That is now Caesars Palace.', '"Street,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Growing up in California, my best friend was Morris Rabinowitz and we often went to the Yiddish Theater."', '"Best,Friend,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I wanted to be a composer.', '"Wanted,Composer"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"By the end of Pop\'s life I wanted to give something back and when I came on board as his musical director he needed me. I wasn\'t the greatest conductor of the orchestra, but I was hired to conduct Frank Sinatra. He was slowing down, his memory wasn\'t what it had been. But his audience never stopped loving him. He had teleprompters."', '"Life,Me,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'My son has no interest in music other than as a listener. He teaches English to Japanese students.', '"Music,Son,Interest"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'If you don\'t work your brain turns to cheese.', '"Work,Brain,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"The idea of the duets albums was the people who joined Frank Sinatra in each song were themselves successful record artists, I never was. I felt a certain apprehension at the time that some people thought my being there was pure nepotism. I felt kind of out of place about that."', '"Time,Song,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I have to do what I have to do like everyone does.', '"Everyone,Like,Does"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Rock \'n\' roll, for me, is another award for underachievers. It is nothing but a testament to mediocrity."', '"Me,Award,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I never felt that it was in anyone\'s best interest to be looked at differently by other people because of a name. I kept to myself a lot.', '"Best,Myself,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Over all these years, I have never had a hit movie, never had a hit television programme and never had a hit record. To my way of thinking, that means success has not been achieved. I have made no mark of my own creation. This is something to be considered."', '"Success,Thinking,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When I was younger, sure, I wanted to have some degree of, shall we say, identity. But it never came."', '"Identity,Never,Degree"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"The way I see it, before I can sell an audience Frank Sr, I have to sell them Frank Jr first."', '"Way,See,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"It pleases me that Frank Sinatra\'s music still has an audience, because many people who have come into the music world and then passed out of the music world are long since forgotten. He has been able to enjoy this great longevity."', '"Music,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When I was a young person, they used to refer to it as Christmas time. Course now it has to be politically correct and call it the holidays."', '"Time,Christmas,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'It\'s amazing the number of young people who are interested in Frank Sinatra.', '"Amazing,People,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I like the Suncoast so much. It is miles from the Strip. It reminds me of the old Vegas atmosphere when things were a little more personal.', '"Me,Old,Miles"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'KKJZ is a very famous jazz station and there aren\'t many more around like them.', '"Famous,Jazz,More"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m very happy to have people say I sound like Frank Sinatra.', '"People,Happy,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I mean, Frank Sinatra is one of the great performers in pop music history. Why shouldn\'t I be delighted to carry on his tradition?"', '"History,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Heidi Fleiss I befriended because she and I went through something of the same nature. And when word reached the tabloids, bless their little hearts, they decided here was something they could make money with."', '"Nature,Money,She"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Sinatra had deep loyalties to his friends for years.', '"Deep,Friends,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Before the State of Israel became a reality, Sinatra was a strong supporter, knowing that Jews were being denied access to the Holy Land. Sinatra met and had a friendship with Israel\'s first Prime Minister David Ben-Gurion. Ben-Gurion gave Sinatra a beautiful Old Testament bible that was a proud possession that my father kept all his life."', '"Life,Friendship,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Sinatra was bothered with issues of anti-Semitism and racism all his life. The song and film he made \'The House I Live In,\' was a deep message against prejudice and he was very proud to have recorded the song."', '"Life,Song,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"We went through rock \'n\' roll, which then became just rock, then punk rock, then the worst disease of all - rap music. It\'s an oxymoron, because rap is not music."', '"Music,Worst,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Rap is the pulsation given by some, usually an electronic rhythm section, without any tonality, and you have someone reading high-school poetry."', '"Poetry,Someone,Reading"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Very few people rise that high, to be a performer known as only one name. Caruso... Valentino... Hitchcock... Garbo."', '"People,Rise,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I always loved the motion picture scores and the great film composers like Elmer Bernstein.', '"Great,Picture,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"The first time people come to see me, it\'s usually because they\'re curious. Then maybe some of them return. I look out in the audience and see the same faces, the same wonderful, loyal faces."', '"Time,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I studied music from the time I was 5.', '"Time,Music,Studied"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I just hope that people remember what I did well, that I gave it everything I had."', '"Hope,Remember,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I think in my generation, when I came along in the early \'60s, the type of music that was in vogue in society in those days had moved on to another kind of music. I was trying to sell antiques in a modern appliance store."', '"Music,Society,Generation"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Elvis Presley was rock \'n\' roll, I thought that was pretty mediocre. But since that time, the succeeding steps in music has been down, just more degradation. Then we got into punk rock, and now we are into rap music, which is a total oxymoron."', '"Time,Music,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Jimmy Van Heusen was a top security test pilot in World War II as well as being a great songwriter. He was absolutely incredible. Van Heusen inspired me to write music.', '"War,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'There is no demand for Frank Sinatra Jr. records. There never has been.', '"Never,Demand,Frank"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Nelson Riddle was really something. Just something else.', '"Something,Just,Riddle"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'A lotta years I was out there on the road pulling one-nighters. Then I got hired to sing in Sam Donahue\'s band in 1963. I was 19 years old.', '"Road,Old,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Life is not positive or negative; it\'s a mixture.', '"Positive,Life,Negative"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Look, as a child growing up it occurred to me that I had everything I could have wanted: a roof over my head, education, food. All of it because my father provided... My way of giving back was being that invisible guy. Giving something back from a lifetime of taking."', '"Education,Food,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m an individual.', 'Individual', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'My father was the kind of man who liked to hang out.', '"Man,Father,Hang"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"It depends on the material. Sometimes I sound like him, sometimes not. There are certain tunes we do that are so familiar to the audience that to perform them without making them sound like Frank Sinatra would be wrong."', '"Sometimes,Sound,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I envy guys who can write funny.', '"Funny,Envy,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"In my own career, I used to do a Sinatra medley in every show, or at least sing one of his songs."', '"My Own,Own,Show"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"It\'s not an easy task, believe me. How the hell do you replace Frank Sinatra? There\'s no way anybody can do that. But as far as I\'m concerned, if there is music to be made and I have to wear somebody else\'s clothes, I can\'t think of anybody\'s I\'d rather wear."', '"Music,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"This business of fame - when people ask me what it was like growing up in this famous family, I say, \'When you take it seriously you\'re in a lot of trouble.\'"', '"Family,Business,Famous"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Van Heusen understood Sinatra\'s style of singing; Sinatra understood Van Heusen\'s concept of melody.', '"Style,Singing,Melody"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Since my father\'s death, a lot of people have made it clear that they\'re not ready to give up the music. For me, it\'s a big, fat gift. I get to sing with a big orchestra and get to sing orchestrations that will never be old."', '"Death,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Never had a hit movie or hit TV show or hit record. I just had visions of doing the best quality of music. Now there is a place for me because Frank Sinatra is dead. They want me to play the music. If it wasn\'t for that, I wouldn\'t be noticed. The only satisfaction is that I do what I do well. That\'s the only lawful satisfaction."', '"Best,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I was never a success.', '"Success,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When I started as a kid, I wanted to be a piano player and songwriter. I only became a singer by accident."', '"Only,Piano,Singer"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'For a thoroughbred to age is never a graceful process.', '"Age,Process,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I began to become very infatuated at the creation of my own music rather than someone else\'s and my piano teacher used to get really cross with me because of the fact that I wasn\'t studying my lessons, I was writing things of my own."', '"Teacher,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"They used to have a saying among the musicians on staff when I was with him, \'Sinatra never does anything the same way once.\' He was a perfectionist, he was a taskmaster and he knew exactly what it was he wanted because he understood how to deliver his message to the audience; never was there a greater example of that than that man."', '"Man,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I believe that when you keep yourself working, you keep yourself alive."', '"Believe,Yourself,Alive"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Mo Ostin was a great money-maker, but he had the aesthetic interest of a fire plug."', '"Great,Fire,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Originally, what we call rock \'n\' roll was nothing more than an attempt of very bad white performers to sound like black rhythm-and-blues performers. They did their best to emulate, they did their best to paraphrase. And that started what later became rock \'n\' roll."', '"Best,Black,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When I was a kid in the 6th grade and first learned how to dance with a girl, we had a record called \'Shake Rattle and Roll,\' made by a group called Bill Haley and His Comets: \'Get out in that kitchen and rattle them pots and pans.\' It was all about mundane things."', '"Dance,Kitchen,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"The Beatles never got through to all ages, nor did Elvis Presley, or any of the other monuments of mediocrity that we\'ve had."', '"Never,Monuments,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I was with him, coincidentally, on the evening in 1979 when they had buried John Wayne. My father cried like a baby when he went to see the Duke."', '"Evening,Father,See"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"There\'s only one Sinatra. But don\'t forget that there\'s only one Sinatra Jr., too."', '"Forget,Only,Too"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"Of course, it\'s human nature for people, when they meet me to have some preconceptions about how I look, how I sing, how I behave. I can understand that. And I\'ve realized you can\'t do anything about human nature except to ignore it."', '"Nature,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"If I can just continue to work and be at least requested to work, I consider that a victory."', '"Work,Victory,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m just a traveling musician.', '"Just,Musician,Traveling"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When Sinatra was alive and singing, he was constantly changing orchestrators from one album to the next because he said he didn\'t want every record to sound like every other record."', '"Singing,Alive,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Frank Sinatra Jr. has never been particularly popular as a record seller.', '"Never,Frank,Record"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'d love to have my own T V. series so I could stay put for awhile.', '"Love,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I know that somewhere deep down I have the ability to act. I just need a chance to prove it.', '"Chance,Know,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Ever since I\'ve been old enough to shave I\'ve been playing clubs.', '"Enough,Old,Playing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'On the road I don\'t shave until the evening before I go out on stage.', '"Evening,Road,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I\'m a singer, not a talker I took singing lessons, not talking lessons."', '"Singing,Not Talking,Talking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'You can only guide children so far.', '"Children,Far,Guide"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I don\'t really look for material with the idea it might make a hit record.', '"Look,Hit,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When I work a nightclub, I dress up in evening wear. There\'s a certain elegance to it all and I like that."', '"Work,Evening,Dress"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'There is a common misconception that when you\'re a singer working for a recording company you get to pick everything you\'re doing. Very few people have been accorded such a luxury.', '"People,Company,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'My father never had to deal with a territory band.', '"Father,Never,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m just an itinerant singer.', '"Just,Singer"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m just down to earth.', '"Earth,Down To Earth,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I have never been a person to build empires.', '"Never,Person,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I just try to fit into society the best I can. Be unobtrusive, be smooth. I don\'t want to hurt anybody, or be hurt."', '"Best,Society,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"In the impetuousness of youth, when you\'re 21 years old, you want results yesterday."', '"Youth,Yesterday,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'It\'s a learning experience to work with my father.', '"Work,Experience,Learning"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"That\'s what I do: I\'m a singer. I have many arrangers, but I usually conduct for myself."', '"Myself,Singer,Conduct"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I\'m studying musical arts, all the way to composition. But I\'m also studying theater arts, stage directing and acting."', '"Way,Acting,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'My father is a really big man.', '"Man,Father,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'My father doesn\'t dislike all newsmen. He has many friends among them. The trouble is the ones who hate him make the headlines.', '"Hate,Father,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I don\'t think a man should be alone all his life. But I want to be ready for marriage I want it to be a lasting thing.', '"Life,Alone,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'It\'s regrettable that some people have to make a substantial living at others\' expense.', '"People,Living,Some People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I spend a lot of time visiting friends, watching video cassette movies, and things like that."', '"Time,Movies,Watching"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'m just grateful to have a job. There are an awful lot of talented performers out there who are out of work.', '"Work,Grateful,Job"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"When you\'re the son of someone who is very famous and you enter the same business, you got to work three times as hard as anyone."', '"Work,Business,Famous"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"I enjoy what I do so much. There\'s people out there who don\'t like what they do, but I\'m fortunate. I have nothing to complain about."', '"People,Nothing,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'Frank Sinatra will go on forever.', '"Will,Forever,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'The best way to get noticed is to take someone that everyone loves and admires and knock him.', '"Best,Way,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"My work happens to be singing, and I love bringing great songs to the attention of my audiences."', '"Love,Work,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', '"As a young singer, a record company wanted me to be a rock singer. I told them I couldn\'t because I didn\'t understand the music."', '"Music,Me,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5d', 'I\'ve been hanging around movie sets and recording studios since I can remember.', '"Remember,I Can,Recording"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5e', '"If you hear Bing Crosby trying to swing, it doesn\'t work. He swings like a rusty gate."', '"Work,Gate,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5e', '"Recording an album and doing it live are like two different animals. There are some people that are great singers live, horrible in the studio."', '"Great,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5e', '"One night I was standing on Third Avenue playing my guitar, when this big Irish policeman came strolling by, and stopped to listen to my singing and playing. When I was done, he politely handed me a ticket for disturbing the peace, while at the same time telling me how much he liked my voice. I wish I still had that ticket."', '"Time,Peace,Guitar"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5e', '"If you get married, you become vulnerable."', '"Become,Get,Vulnerable"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', 'What you see is what you see.', '"See,You"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', 'I don\'t like to say I have given my life to art. I prefer to say art has given me my life.', '"Life,Art,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"But, after all, the aim of art is to create space - space that is not compromised by decoration or illustration, space within which the subjects of painting can live."', '"Space,Art,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"No art is any good unless you can feel how it\'s put together. By and large it\'s the eye, the hand and if it\'s any good, you feel the body. Most of the best stuff seems to be a complete gesture, the totality of the artist\'s body; you can really lean on it."', '"Best,Good,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"Up until 35 I had a slightly skewed world view. I honestly believed everybody in the world wanted to make abstract paintings, and people only became lawyers and doctors and brokers and things because they couldn\'t make abstract paintings."', '"View,World,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', 'A sculpture is just a painting cut out and stood up somewhere.', '"Painting,Somewhere,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"Architecture can\'t fully represent the chaos and turmoil that are part of the human personality, but you need to put some of that turmoil into the architecture, or it isn\'t real."', '"Architecture,Personality,Chaos"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"I was worried in the \'80s that the best abstract painting had become obsessed with materiality, and painterly gestures and materiality were up against the wall."', '"Best,Painting,Abstract"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', 'One learns about painting by looking at and imitating other painters.', '"Painting,Looking,About"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"When I\'m painting the picture, I\'m really painting a picture. I may have a flat-footed technique, or something like that, but still, to me, the thrill, or the meat of the thing, is the actual painting. I don\'t get any thrill out of laying it out."', '"Me,Painting,Picture"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', 'I want to make exalted art. A successful image has pictorial lift. I am looking for whatever is up there.', '"Art,I Am,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe5f', '"I don\'t like a lot of the stuff that goes on in the art world, but it\'s hard to be old and like what goes on around you."', '"Art,World,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe60', 'I got into a fight with Walt Disney: I always pick the wrong people to fight with.', '"Fight,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe60', '"That was the big secret. Walt would do things over and over again, with no regard to money, to get things perfect."', '"Money,Perfect,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe60', '"There\'s always been some moron-who usually went by the name of \'producer\' - who would have to justify his existence, and interfere."', '"Name,Always,Interfere"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"A Home Run Derby is fun. It\'s just like taking batting practice, and you just want to go deep. Guys do it every day. Yes, there\'s a little more pressure when they pull that cage back, but if you practice properly, it shouldn\'t affect the second half of your season at all."', '"Home,Fun,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"At the Home Run Derby, you\'re expected to hit home runs. You\'re up there trying to hit home runs."', '"Home,Trying,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', 'Doing something the right way is something I take pride in.', '"Pride,Way,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', 'I think there is a lot of good in making the All-Star Team. People look at your career a little bit differently.', '"Good,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"I got snubbed about eight times for the Mid-Summer Classic, and I know what type of career I had, and I know that I\'m a true All-Star. The selection process is not very accurate."', '"Process,True,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"I grew up in the Boys & Girls Club. That\'s where I really started playing all sports, and that\'s why I\'m a big advocate for the work they do."', '"Work,Sports,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"In the South, the food is outstanding. Down south, we eat to get full, and the people up north, they don\'t do that."', '"Food,People,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"When you\'re going into a game, you\'re not expected to hit a home run every game. You\'re just doing everything proper with proper swings."', '"Home,Game,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', 'I come from good stock. Both of my parents are big - my dad is a big guy; my mom is a big lady.', '"Good,Mom,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe61', '"I\'m just happy to be sitting right here in Chicago and right here at U.S. Cellular Field, holding my Hall of Fame press conference. I\'m proud of that."', '"Happy,Proud,Fame"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"A person whose skin is metallic can no more have its reproduction restricted than a black-skinned person. Regarding life as a form of machinery and intelligent machines as people without our environmental limitations is essential in understanding FAP, the Final Anthropic Principle, which deals with evolution in the far future."', '"Life,Future,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"We physicists know that a beautiful postulate is more likely to be correct than an ugly one. Why not adopt this Postulate of Eternal Life, at least as a working hypothesis?"', '"Life,Beautiful,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"Whether the ice caps melt, or expand - whatever happens - the anthropogenic global warming theorists claim it confirms their theory. A perfect example of a pseudo-science like astrology."', '"Perfect,Global Warming,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"If any reader has lost a loved one or is afraid of death, modern physics says: \'Be comforted, you and they shall live again.\'"', '"Death,Lost,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', 'The Omega Point Theory can be a solid foundation of support for all of the great human religions.', '"Great,Support,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"A scientist... must accept the results of experiment, and nothing but the results of experiment."', '"Nothing,Accept,Experiment"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"By the last decades of the 21st century, church worship will still take the form of reading passages of traditional texts - the Bible, the Koran, the Rig Veda - but physicist-priests will preside over the ceremonies."', '"Bible,Will,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"Future generations will know there\'s nothing mystical about wetware because by 2100, Moore\'s law will have given us tiny quantum computers powerful enough to upload a human soul."', '"Future,Computers,Soul"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"Human uploads have such a natural advantage over present-day people in the environment of space, it\'s exceedingly unlikely flesh-and-blood beings will ever engage in interstellar travel."', '"Space,Travel,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"Either theology is pure nonsense, a subject with no content, or else theology must ultimately become a branch of physics."', '"Physics,Nonsense,Pure"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', '"What you can show using physics, forces this universe to continue to exist. As long as you\'re using general relativity and quantum mechanics you are forced to conclude that God exists."', '"God,Long,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe62', 'The core of all religions is a belief in a supreme personal god.', '"God,All Religions,Belief"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"My son, Tony Vincent, is a stuntman. He doubles for Jim Caviezel on \'Person of Interest.\' He works really hard."', '"Son,Person,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Sometimes people start with you. Especially in local places - \'Hey, go get your shine box.\' So I go out earlier. I wear sunglasses and a cap... That\'s the downside of being successful."', '"Sunglasses,Shine,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"A man\'s man is respectful, he\'s honorable, he\'s loyal, he\'s sensitive, he\'s strong, he\'s tough, he\'s well-groomed, he has a sense of humor - and he takes care of himself and his lady."', '"Humor,Man,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'Grooming should be done in moderation.', '"Done,Grooming,Moderation"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"If you decide to go clubbing on a Friday night, and you\'re home before two A.M., you\'re not a man\'s man."', '"Home,Night,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"\'The Godfather\' illustrated the family values - the reality that it was really a family thing, honor and tradition. It wasn\'t just a single-dimension thing."', '"Family,Reality,Honor"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'David Chase is a genius.', '"Genius,Chase,David"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I\'m not saying \'The Godfather\' trilogy was bad - because it was brilliant - but that was fiction. It was based on reality.', '"Reality,Bad,Brilliant"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Bad boys are classy and refined. For example, even though Donald Trump came from money and a privileged lifestyle, he\'s a man\'s man."', '"Money,Classy,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I\'m a cigar person, I don\'t smoke one every day, but I used to smoke them, and I had my own cigar at one time. So, I\'m fairly knowledgeable about that."', '"Time,Day,Smoke"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I think \'The Sopranos\' probably solidifies the misconception that people have about New Jersey to begin with. Because you\'re from Jersey, and everybody has an accent, you are perceived a certain way. I don\'t know if they are jealous or in awe or look down their nose at you, but that\'s the way life is. If you don\'t like it, change the channel."', '"Life,Change,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I remember playing in Union City, and we had crap games after we finished playing at night. We would go next door to the cab stand where they were playing gin rummy and betting $1,000 a hand."', '"Night,City,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Chicago - it\'s the Midwest, and the people are not as tough or not as edgy as they are in New York."', '"Tough,New,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I knew so many gangsters, and I call on that experience with them for characters."', '"Experience,Call,Knew"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'You take what God gives you and relish it.', '"God,Take,Relish"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"You establish a technique on how to develop characters. Everyone does it their own way, and that\'s what makes it fun."', '"Fun,Way,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'We define a metrosexual as someone who really takes care of themselves in terms of grooming and style. There is nothing wrong with that. But I think you need to have some other values. It\'s cool to incorporate some traditional values into metrosexuality. Then it becomes a good lifestyle.', '"Cool,Good,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"As far as music is concerned, I played music for a very long time, so I have a background in that."', '"Time,Music,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Steve Van Zandt is a very intelligent, smart guy. He\'s a historian, he knows a lot about rock n\' roll, a lot about music."', '"Music,Smart,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I think all the roles were something that sort of hit me, and I guess I was very lucky to get those roles."', '"Me,Guess,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"People approach you in a different way when you\'re a celebrity - some are nice, some are not nice."', '"Way,People,Celebrity"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I\'ve met a lot of big stars who have humility. Sly Stallone is a very humble guy. Robert DeNiro is a really humble guy. Some of the women aren\'t so humble for some reason. I don\'t know why.', '"Women,Humble,Stars"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"When lines are great, they\'re easy to do. You just find the essence of it, and you do it."', '"Great,Easy,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I think that all the time I lived alone changed me.', '"Alone,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'Being down makes you think who you are.', '"Down,Think,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Actors are real egomaniacs. They get into a movie, they think the whole movie\'s about them."', '"Real,Think,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"There was an article about me once, and the first line was, \'It\'s good to be a gangster.\' Well, I\'m not a gangster. I\'m an actor."', '"Good,Me,Gangster"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"As a character actor, you have to understand that it\'s not about you. You have to remember it\'s about someone else\'s life. And your character is just passing through."', '"Life,Character,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"People are fascinated with the fast life, the easy life. For some reason, that\'s an American dream, and it goes all the way back to the Edward G. Robinsons and the Cagneys."', '"Life,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"A man\'s man has no problems with commitment, as long as he\'s not with a woman who needs to be committed."', '"Man,Long,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Fellas, it\'s all a numbers game. The more women you meet, the greater chance you have of finding the right one."', '"Women,Chance,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Fellas, one of the most effective ways to meet a woman is on the street."', '"Woman,Street,Meet"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'Atkins - I was on that for two weeks. All I lost was 14 days.', '"Lost,Two,Days"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'It\'s very important what you say to kids. You have to walk a very fine line between talking about your life and talking about what you\'ve done.', '"Life,Walk,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '\'The Godfather\' changed the way gangsters acted.', '"Way,Changed,Godfather"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"My wife and I lived in Chicago for two months, and we went to a lot of great restaurants."', '"Great,Wife,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'New York\'s got a little rougher edge to it than Chicago.', '"New,Edge,Little"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I never in my wildest dreams thought that I\'d have merchandise selling on a web site. It\'s just amazing to me.', '"Dreams,Amazing,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I am a musician by rights, and I played in Asbury Park in the old African Room in the Robert Trent Hotel next to the Albion. That was in the early \'60s."', '"I Am,Hotel,Room"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I wanted to be what I am. All my life. A musician and an actor.', '"Life,I Am,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"You are you, and nobody else can do what you do. But a little talent can help."', '"Talent,Nobody,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I played the Holiday Motel on the circle in 1970. I know the Jersey Shore.', '"Circle,Know,Holiday"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"If it\'s Saturday night, and you\'re sitting on your couch watching \'Showtime at the Apollo,\' then you\'re not a man\'s man."', '"Night,Man,Watching"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"You have got to have a good sense of humor, you have got to be tough, and you have got to know how to dress."', '"Good,Humor,Dress"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'People are funny in the way that they choose to express themselves.', '"Funny,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'I did a lot of \'NYPD Blues\' and \'Law & Orders\' and a couple of other ones that were shot in New York earlier in my career.', '"Law,New,Blues"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"There\'s a moment of truth that comes when you are performing, and you are all alone."', '"Alone,Truth,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'Nothing is real until you walk out on stage.', '"Walk,Nothing,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I don\'t know what drives me. I need to work. I wanted to be in the entertainment field, but I didn\'t know what."', '"Work,Me,Entertainment"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', 'You see mob guys when you play in nightclubs. It\'s part of the protocol.', '"See,Play,Mob"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I do a lot of meet-and-greets with the people, and I do \'sign shows\' where I meet people and sign autographs."', '"People,Meet,Where"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I enjoy going to the beach, relaxing with my wife, going out to dinner, and having a good time."', '"Time,Good,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"When you\'re acting on camera, you don\'t really think of your voice. You think of the whole instrument - your body, your look, and whatever you have to do. But when you\'re doing the voiceover, you\'re thinking only of your voice. You really can\'t compare the two different mediums."', '"Thinking,Look,Body"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I work on television and I work in film, and the acting is two different things."', '"Work,Acting,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"When I was 18 years old and playing the drums, I never thought that I would have a website and that people will be buying my autographed picture and paying money for it."', '"Money,Picture,People"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"I spent my youth playing music, and I worked a lot in New Jersey and New York clubs. At 18, I worked all around Hudson, Essex, and Bergen counties."', '"Music,Youth,New"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe64', '"Trust is very important. In \'Goodfellas\' in the \'Go home and get your shine box!\' scene, we must have filmed 15 takes. If you played each take back, the timing would be exactly the same each time."', '"Trust,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"You reach for the stars and you work your butt off to achieve your dreams. If you fall short, you fall short, but you say you gave it your best."', '"Dreams,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'Be thirsty to always try to achieve something more.', '"Always,Achieve,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I met my wife here. I had my first daughter here in Boston.', '"Wife,Daughter,First"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'We don\'t want to give up free throws. Those are mistakes.', '"Free,Mistakes,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Winning two in a row doesn\'t seem like a big deal, but when you haven\'t done it in three months, it\'s a big deal."', '"Winning,Done,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:02:00', '2023-05-29 12:02:00'),
	('398925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I\'m a very competitive person and losing doesn\'t sit well with me.', '"Me,Losing,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"A player-led team is better than a coach-led team, no doubt."', '"Better,Doubt,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I\'m very good at blocking out noise.', '"Good,Noise,Blocking"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Well, any teacher or coach derives his greatest pleasure in their profession or their process when they see their pupil succeed, so I would say I definitely enjoy that part of the game."', '"Teacher,Game,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I was giving everything I had to classes, and I was getting a 2.6. I knew that wasn\'t going to get me into med school."', '"Me,School,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I\'m sort of an optimist, a high energy type of enthusiastic guy. Someone that tries to be genuine with the players, I\'m not a guy that\'s going to come in and be a drill sergeant."', '"Energy,Genuine,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I was sort of obsessed with the Phillies as a young kid.', '"Young,Kid,Sort"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'What I would say is every assistant coach in the NBA wants to be head coach.', '"Head,Say,Coach"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'Mom and Dad were the best. I never clashed with them.', '"Best,Mom,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"As a coach, you have to play to how your team is built."', '"Your,Play,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'Nobody impacts winning more than LeBron James.', '"Winning,Nobody,More"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'One of the hidden benefits of me being a student manager at Kentucky was me having the responsibility of driving Rick Pitino to his motivational speaking engagements.', '"Motivational,Me,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"It was larger than life - the 76ers, Dr. J, Moses Malone, Mo Cheeks, Andrew Toney and Bobby Jones - those were the teams that I grew up following."', '"Life,Cheeks,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I did feel support right from the start from LeBron. He\'s always shown me a great deal of respect dating back to our battles when I was in Indiana and competing with the Heat in the conference finals, and coaching him in the All-Star Game."', '"Respect,Great,Dating"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'There\'s a lot of different ways to be successful in college basketball. Most of it stems from talent and having the ability to recruit.', '"Talent,Ability,College"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I\'ve got a lot of coaching friends in the business, in basketball and in other sports, that really when you talk about choosing jobs, you want to make sure that you have a strong ownership group and the reputation of the DeVos family is as good as it goods."', '"Family,Business,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I don\'t like isolation play, unless you\'re in the low post."', '"Isolation,Play,Low"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Everybody wants to beat their former team, and I\'m no different."', '"Beat,Former,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'We watched a show called \'Outer Banks\' which was really good.', '"Good,Show,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Phil Jackson is a role model, and basically a coaching idol of mine. He\'s someone I really tried to model some of my coaching philosophies after."', '"Role Model,Someone,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"When you have your roster set up different ways, you really just have to examine the roster, find out what their strengths and weakness are and hopefully you take your roster and the vision you want to implement of how you want to play and you can tweak your roster to create that."', '"Vision,Create,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I have nothing but positive feelings about the Pacers.', '"Positive,Feelings,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'What\'s important to us is developing the habit of playing harder than our opponent every night.', '"Night,Habit,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"To have the ability to not have to change your lineup every night - if you\'re playing a big team, you don\'t have to take your smalls out; and if you are playing a small team, you don\'t have to pull your bigs. When you have bigs who are versatile and can play both styles then you can stay true to who you are every night."', '"Change,Night,True"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Every player that I\'ve ever been around that\'s worth a damn wants to be challenged and wants to be pushed, and wants to be coached hard, and wants to be held accountable."', '"Worth,Hard,Damn"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'A lot of the better offenses sacrifice defense to be a good offense and I\'m not interested in doing that.', '"Good,Sacrifice,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I think players have ups and downs in their careers.', '"Ups And Downs,Players,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I like playing size per position defensively.', '"Position,Size,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I love offensive physicality.', '"Love,Offensive,Physicality"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'It\'s tough to get wings deep post catches when you\'re playing with two bigs all the time.', '"Time,Wings,Tough"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I\'m an optimist by nature.', '"Nature,Optimist"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The city of Orlando has so much to offer.', '"City,Offer,Much"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"My wife and I grew up in the Northeast but my daughters are sort of small-town girls, from the Midwest."', '"Wife,Up,Daughters"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I hope to create a culture here in Orlando where we\'re winning and we\'re having fun doing it.', '"Hope,Culture,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I graduated in biology by overcoming an incredibly impossible science workload in college. The knowledge does nothing for me, but knowing I achieved that makes me feel like I can achieve anything because those science classes in biology are just impossible."', '"Science,Knowledge,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I had a persistent mindset that I was going to make something happen for myself.', '"Myself,Mindset,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The NBA? Never in my wildest dreams when I was playing in Division III basketball.', '"Dreams,Never,Division"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I was just thankful to be a student manager, and if that led to a high school coaching job or maybe I could stick at a small Division I school as an assistant, that would have been a success for me."', '"Success,Thankful,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I was playing division three basketball and I wanted to find a way to work in basketball full-time. The way to do that was not in division three right away; you\'d have to be a part-time assistant or whatever. So, I made the decision to transfer to Kentucky. Just so I could get my feet wet and maybe get a job in D-1."', '"Work,Decision,Feet"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I think every coach brings their own personality.', '"Personality,Own,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The state of Florida is an attractive place to live.', '"Live,Place,Attractive"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I\'ve always been of the mindset that relationships can be different and relationships can go bad with different people. That doesn\'t mean they\'re going to be a bad relationship with me.', '"Relationship,Me,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I feel like winning starts with defense and rebounding.', '"Winning,Feel,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"The value in having bigs that have the ability to shoot from the perimeter has increased and having bigs that have the defensive versatility to not only protect the rim, but to switch out and defend smaller guards, the value of that has also increased."', '"Value,Shoot,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"There are a lot of 7-footers that aren\'t good shot blockers whether it\'s their athleticism, their quick jump, their eye-hand coordination, their ability to get their hands on the ball. Part of it is just instinctual."', '"Good,Hands,Jump"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'Too many young guys on one team isn\'t good.', '"Good,Young,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'You work hard and you drill daily all the habits that you need to win at basketball and you\'re going to create a winning culture.', '"Work,Daily,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I\'m not from Philly - I\'m from South Jersey, but we still consider that the Philly area."', '"Still,Philly,Jersey"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"If you commit to the defensive end of the floor, you\'re going to have a chance to win every night. And if you\'re a great defensive team, you\'re going to go to the playoffs."', '"Great,Chance,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"No, I don\'t think you can ever worry about playing not to get hurt. I think that\'s when you get hurt."', '"Worry,Hurt,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I think there\'s a danger in letting someone else shape how you\'re going to approach a player. Every person has somebody who\'s going to say something negative about them, you know? If you pay attention to all that stuff instead of seeing it for your own eyes, you can miss out on some opportunities."', '"Eyes,Negative,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I really think your roster and your personnel dictates your style of play. When you have David West and Roy Hibbert does it make sense to play spread pick-and-roll game when you have those abilities inside?', '"Game,Style,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"From Game A to Game B, your whole focus is on improving your team and what is the next challenge. What does the next team present? What are the solutions to the puzzle?"', '"Focus,Game,Puzzle"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"You spend your entire time 24 hours a day thinking about when is the next game, and you put together the plan and that\'s a lot of fun. When the game\'s ready to go, it\'s just exciting to see how all your studying is going to pay off."', '"Time,Together,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I grew up the No. 1 Michael Jordan fan on Earth. I was from the Philadelphia area and Jordan was king.', '"King,Earth,Fan"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"The Lakers have always been on the forefront and anywhere LeBron has been, has been on the forefront."', '"Always,Anywhere,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I feel that each opportunity has been a learning experience for me and will help me grow and be a better coach here in L.A.', '"Experience,Learning,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Growing up in South Jersey, I have always been an Eagles fan. I don\'t paint my face or anything like that, but I deeply care about the team."', '"Face,Care,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'It\'s always great to compete against the 76ers and to have friends and family watch.', '"Family,Great,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Paul George is just a gifted guy that has versatility that no one else in the league has - in terms of playing ones, twos of threes, and really just blanket another team\'s top perimeter scorer."', '"Versatility,Top,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Charge-taking can be one effective way to affect the rim, but the whistle\'s gonna blow a lot."', '"Way,Affect,Gonna"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'You got to worry about getting good damn coaches.', '"Good,Worry,Damn"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I am a positive-energy, enthusiasm type of a coach and I\'m going to spread that to everybody that will feel it."', '"I Am,Feel,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I was at a basketball camp when I was a kid and the lecturer used basketball spinning to teach us a lesson on never being satisfied with what you\'ve accomplished. The lecturer talked about how the game of basketball was about learning to control the ball through dribbling and passing and shooting.', '"Learning,Game,Control"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'Coaching in the NBA is a tough trick.', '"Tough,Coaching,Trick"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I always want to help people that are in need.', '"People,Help,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I actually missed some assignments at Kentucky because my teachers were like, \'Didn\'t you check your e-mail?\' I was like, \'I don\'t really know how to use e-mail.\'"', '"Know,Your,Teachers"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'You\'ve got to stay away from those plays that zap your energy.', '"Energy,Your,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The Orlando Magic is a great organization.', '"Great,Organization,Magic"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"With all the talk of the 3-point line, it\'s still most important to build your defense inside to out."', '"Important,Talk,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"A lot of times those things are shaped by coaches you work with, but other times they\'re shaped by coaches you admire and study."', '"Work,Admire,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Focus on things you can control. Things that are out of control, you can\'t worry about what the result is going to be, you just focus on trying to do the best in your situation that you can."', '"Best,Focus,Result"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Sometimes, you have to take a big risk."', '"Sometimes,Big,Risk"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I played a lot of sports growing up. I played soccer.', '"Sports,Growing Up,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('398999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"The film room teaches you how to do the job, how to study the game, how to teach the game from film. How to create an advantage for your team by knowing your opponent, and all their plays and tendencies. And there\'s no better guy in the world that I\'ve been around than Jim O\'Brien at breaking down film."', '"World,Game,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Every great basketball team, every team that\'s on a championship journey takes steps each year, taking a step further than they were the year before."', '"Great,Journey,Step"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"You coach your own system for so many years, that\'s all you ever know. To be able to step inside and see how others do it was very beneficial."', '"Step,See,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The value of a Bismack Biyombo is the speed and agility that he has at the center position.', '"Value,Speed,Position"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I\'ve got a lot of belief in Aaron Gordon and he\'s one of the reasons that I took the job here with the Magic. When a guy cares as much as he does and works as hard as he does, that impacts the group. And that type of attitude is infectious."', '"Attitude,Magic,Belief"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Aaron Gordon, obviously, is a great runner."', '"Great,Gordon,Obviously"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"When you defend and rebound and you trust the pass on the offensive end, you\'re going to have the ability to win a lot of games."', '"Trust,Win,End"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I really wanted to stay in Indiana forever, but this is a business and you\'ve got to respect the decisions that are made."', '"Respect,Business,Forever"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"You compete to win games, but the people that you meet and are able to help, develop and grow - that\'s the most rewarding part of this job."', '"Grow,People,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I love watching game tape. I can do it all day long and enjoy every minute of it.', '"Love,Game,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"When you have the confidence that you can go four, five, six possessions where you\'re just squeezing the other team\'s offense, getting stops, and then with our ability to run the floor, with LeBron James being the quarterback of that action and being in attack mode, we have a strong belief in what we can accomplish as a group."', '"Confidence,Action,Belief"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"If you have an elite defense, that can be your third star, so to speak."', '"Speak,Elite,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'I liked medicine. I liked helping people. I liked the biology of it and understanding how the body works.', '"Body,People,Biology"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"You don\'t ever really wanna be let go from a job, but like anything that happens in life, you gotta make the best of your situation."', '"Life,Best,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"When I do get in that environment around other coaches, I do have an extra bounce in my step."', '"Step,Bounce,Environment"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'You never know who you\'re going to see there during a Lakers game.', '"Game,See,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', 'The reason that I met my wife was because the lockout of \'99. There were about six months where there was no film and no work and I had a social life.', '"Life,Work,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"This is a very stressful profession. Not just coaching, but head coaching at this level with all of the variables that you have on your mind 24/7, it does take a toll on your health and you have to be very cognizant about what\'s going on with your body and listen to your body and make sure that you take care of your body."', '"Health,Mind,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"Being able to step away from your work is big. Not even the actual work of sitting down and looking at game tape, but actually putting your job aside and focusing on other things. That\'s a big part of being successful in this league."', '"Work,Game,Step"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"I thoroughly enjoy this profession and everything that goes into it - from improving your own guys and also the game-planning and studying the opponents. I enjoy that, I really do."', '"Everything,Own,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe65', '"When we lose, watching a game tape is therapeutic for me because it brings clarity to what happened. And when we win it\'s fun and rewarding to see our guys do what we ask them to do."', '"Me,Game,Lose"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe66', '"The whole westward expansion myth is seen as romantic. But it\'s a joke, a blot on American history."', '"History,Romantic,American"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe66', 'The vast sage desert undulates with almost imperceptible tides like the oceans.', '"Desert,Like,Almost"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe67', '"God made man in his own image, and man returned the favour."', '"God,Man,Image"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe67', '"Monuments are for the living, not the dead."', '"Dead,Living,Monuments"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe67', 'Any fool can have bad luck; the art consists in knowing how to exploit it.', '"Art,Fool,Luck"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe67', 'Virtue looks good but it only suits imposing figures.', '"Good,Looks,Virtue"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe67', 'The laws of this world are for children.', '"World,Children,Laws"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', 'I was voted by my high school senior class as most likely to recede.', '"School,High School,High"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', '"I\'ve been doing voices as long as I can remember. When I was little I could pick up on sounds, and then I discovered you could distort what you hear and make people laugh or disrupt a class."', '"Long,Remember,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', '"One thing that seems to surprise the studios is finding out later my willingness to audition. Under the right circumstances, I actually enjoy it very much."', '"Surprise,Circumstances,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', '"I have worked alone and with a cast and enjoy the process both ways. There is more back-and-forth with a full cast, and you can feed off the other actors\' performance."', '"Alone,Process,Performance"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', 'I have this peculiar ability to be able to anticipate mouth movements on screen and fill them with words or sound.', '"Words,Mouth,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', '"Normally I play dads, good guys, and little animals."', '"Good,Play,Animals"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe68', '"I like looking at the characters. Seeing them always brings up some voice or attitude. I am much more visual, and that works so much better than having someone tell me what the character is all about."', '"Attitude,Character,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe69', 'A nation\'s ability to fight a modern war is as good as its technological ability.', '"War,Good,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe69', '"Gentlemen, I give you the Whittle engine."', '"Engine,Give,Gentlemen"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe69', '"Well, that\'s what it was bloody well designed to do, wasn\'t it?"', '"Well,Bloody,Designed"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe69', 'I had always realized it was desirable to gear down the jet.', '"Always,Down,Gear"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"We can\'t just rail against crime. We must speak of the root problems - devastating family breakup, an insidious culture of violence that cheapens human life, skyrocketing prisoner recidivism rates that rob our communities of husbands and fathers - and recognize that there is a societal role in rehabilitation and restoration."', '"Life,Family,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"There are two kinds of people in America today: those who have experienced a foreign cyber attack and know it, and those who have experienced a foreign cyber attack and don\'t know it."', '"Today,America,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"As a follower of Jesus, I am called to work for justice and reconciliation, and to be an advocate for those who cannot speak for themselves. I plan to focus my future work on human rights and religious freedom - both domestic and international - as well as matters of the culture and the American family."', '"Work,Family,Freedom"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', 'I don\'t think people want to see someone buy a congressional race.', '"People,See,Race"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', 'We\'re not losing the peace.', '"Peace,Losing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', 'Scripture makes it clear to me that there is an obligation to speak out on behalf of those being persecuted.', '"Me,Speak,Clear"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"My hope and prayer is that the body of Christ in America will awake with holy boldness, a boldness content neither with silence nor mere words but that backs up those words with action and results."', '"Hope,Prayer,Silence"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"When you see people suffering and dying and hungry, this job gives you the ability to do something about it."', '"Suffering,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"Having served in the Nixon Administration, I am well aware of how the political leadership of an administration can try to politicize the civil service, including law enforcement."', '"Leadership,Political,Service"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"If there\'s amnesty leading to citizenship, I\'m going to vote against it again."', '"Vote,Citizenship,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"I have been a lifelong stutterer, and when I was young, I experienced some very difficult times."', '"Difficult,Young,Difficult Times"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"I am compelled, because of my faith, to have compassion for the weak and vulnerable in our midst."', '"Faith,I Am,Compassion"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', 'You can\'t just pillory the teachers unions and sound the free market trumpet. We must visit the failing schools. We must talk to the mother who desperately wants more for her child and offer a constructive way out. We can\'t simply lambaste... food stamps or decry dependency.', '"Food,Free,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"Religious freedom, often referred to as the first freedom, is of central import to the American experiment. As such it should feature prominently in U.S. foreign policy."', '"Freedom,American,Experiment"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', 'We need to change the focus from celebrating sales at the mall to celebrating the significance of President Washington\'s birth to the birth of our nation.', '"Change,Focus,Birth"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6a', '"Some people criticize the faithful for getting involved in politics, but it\'s important to remember that down through the centuries, people motivated by their faith have done many important things. Martin Luther King Jr. - motivated by his faith - brought about an end to segregation in our country."', '"Politics,Faith,King"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'I cannot let this opportunity pass without placing on record how much I have enjoyed my cricket with Kent.', '"Opportunity,Cricket,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'In the old days we were probably educated in cricket in a far more serious way than now.', '"Cricket,Way,Serious"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'We always had to play the game and play for the team. It is a Kent tradition.', '"Game,Always,Tradition"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', '"I don\'t think I ever worked harder at any match during my career to get runs as I did then, nor did I ever have to face in one game such consistently fast bowlers as the Australian pair, Gregory and McDonald."', '"Face,Game,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'I was not depressed when they got me out. I have always taken my dismissals as part of the game.', '"Me,Game,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'It is amazing how the public steadfastly refuse to attend the third day of a match when so often the last day produces the best and most exciting cricket.', '"Best,Amazing,Cricket"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'It was never a policy of the Kent team that the pitch must be occupied all day after winning the toss.', '"Day,Winning,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'Lots of times I was out through forcing the game.', '"Game,Through,Forcing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', '"Square cuts which ordinarily would have flashed to the boundary earned only two, and I believe that those two innings would have been worth 150 apiece in a county match."', '"Believe,Worth,I Believe That"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', '"Still, I believe it is only a passing phase and cricket will one day produce an abundance of great players."', '"Great,Believe,Cricket"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6b', 'Those were the great days when plenty of amateurs could spare time for cricket.', '"Time,Great,Cricket"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6c', '"From where they stood, they could see the castle."', '"Castle,See,Where"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6c', '"About fifteen miles above New Orleans the river goes very slowly. It has broadened out there until it is almost a sea and the water is yellow with the mud of half a continent. Where the sun strikes it, it is golden."', '"Water,River,Sun"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6c', '"When it was over, it was not really over, and that was the trouble."', '"Trouble,Over,Over It"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6c', 'There was no wind in all that sweep of sky.', '"Sky,Wind,Sweep"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"Some scientists claim that hydrogen, because it is so plentiful, is the basic building block of the universe. I dispute that. I say there is more stupidity than hydrogen, and that is the basic building block of the universe."', '"Stupidity,Universe,Building"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"You can\'t be a real country unless you have a beer and an airline. It helps if you have some kind of a football team, or some nuclear weapons, but at the very least you need a beer."', '"Football,Country,Beer"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"Most rock journalism is people who can\'t write, interviewing people who can\'t talk, for people who can\'t read."', '"Journalism,People,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"There is more stupidity than hydrogen in the universe, and it has a longer shelf life."', '"Life,Stupidity,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Politics is the entertainment branch of industry.', '"Politics,Entertainment,Industry"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Communism doesn\'t work because people like to own stuff.', '"Work,People,Communism"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Art is making something out of nothing and selling it.', '"Art,Nothing,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"If you want to get laid, go to college. If you want an education, go to the library."', '"Education,Library,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'One of my favorite philosophical tenets is that people will agree with you only if they already agree with you. You do not change people\'s minds.', '"Change,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"Without music to decorate it, time is just a bunch of boring production deadlines or dates by which bills must be paid."', '"Time,Music,Boring"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'There are more love songs than anything else. If songs could make you do something we\'d all love one another.', '"Love,Music,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"The computer can\'t tell you the emotional story. It can give you the exact mathematical design, but what\'s missing is the eyebrows."', '"Design,Story,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"You can\'t always write a chord ugly enough to say what you want to say, so sometimes you have to rely on a giraffe filled with whipped cream."', '"Sometimes,Enough,Ugly"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"It isn\'t necessary to imagine the world ending in fire or ice. There are two other possibilities: one is paperwork, and the other is nostalgia."', '"Fire,World,Ending"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'All the good music has already been written by people with wigs and stuff.', '"Good,Music,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'The United States is a nation of laws: badly written and randomly enforced.', '"Nation,Laws,United"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Most people wouldn\'t know music if it came up and bit them on the ass.', '"Music,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'I never set out to be weird. It was always other people who called me weird.', '"Me,Weird,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"Music, in performance, is a type of sculpture. The air in the performance is sculpted into something."', '"Music,Performance,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Without deviation progress is not possible.', '"Progress,Possible,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"Everybody believes in something and everybody, by virtue of the fact that they believe in something, uses that something to support their own existence."', '"Believe,Support,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'I searched for years I found no love. I\'m sure that love will never be a product of plasticity.', '"Love,No Love,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', '"A composer is a guy who goes around forcing his will on unsuspecting air molecules, often with the assistance of unsuspecting musicians."', '"Will,Air,Molecules"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'No change in musical style will survive unless it is accompanied by a change in clothing style. Rock is to dress up to.', '"Change,Dress,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6d', 'Music is always a commentary on society.', '"Music,Society,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Whoever believes that a symbolic tank parade on the alliance\'s eastern border will bring security is mistaken.', '"Security,Will,Parade"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Are we strong? Can we defend ourselves? Are we standing shoulder to shoulder? Do we stand up for each other?', '"Stand,Stand Up,Standing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Europe\'s demography is developing towards a smaller working population in an ageing society.', '"Society,Europe,Population"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Today, our world is more interconnected than ever. This offers many opportunities; it creates wealth and new freedoms. Yet our world is also vulnerable, full of friction points and conflicts of interest."', '"Today,World,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'I feel that we Germans are spending less and less time talking to each other. And even less time listening to each other.', '"Time,Feel,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Wherever you look - especially on social media - we see hate; there is shouting and daily outrage.', '"Daily,Hate,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Our democracy is as strong as we make it. Its founding principle is that we voice our opinions, and that we are willing to argue for what we believe in."', '"Democracy,Believe,Voice"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Reaching compromise does not signal weakness, but rather is a sign of strength. The ability to compromise is the backbone of democracy."', '"Strength,Democracy,Compromise"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Courage is the lifeblood of democracy.', '"Courage,Democracy,Lifeblood"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"The history of the outbreak of war 100 years ago and of the collapse of the fragile balance of power in Europe in the summer of 1914 is a disturbing tale of the failure of the governing elites and the military, but also of diplomacy."', '"War,History,Failure"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Seventeen million people around the world lost their lives in the first world war, countless suffered and were marred for life."', '"Life,War,World"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Twenty-five years after the fall of the Berlin Walland the lifting of the iron curtain, troublespots abound: the Middle East and parts of Africa lack a stable regional security architecture; in east Asia, nationalist tendencies and competing ambitions are threatening peace and stability in the region and beyond."', '"Peace,Architecture,Security"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Taxing financial markets, promoting research and development, and mobilising investments: that means learning our lessons from the financial market crisis and changing our focus."', '"Learning,Focus,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Resources are becoming scarcer. If we want to promote new growth, we should focus on the quality of the value we are creating."', '"Focus,Growth,Quality"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Europe has the potential to pioneer and supply a sustainable worldwide economy.', '"Europe,Potential,Economy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"The fact is that Germany is taking on its responsibility in the world - in the fight against IS, but also in the Middle East, in Africa and in Afghanistan."', '"Fight,World,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Responsibility is always about concrete action.', '"Responsibility,Action,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Where there is a threat of mass murder, where the stability and order of countries and entire regions are endangered, and where there is no chance of successful political settlements without military support, we must be willing to honestly weigh up the risks of getting involved against the consequences of doing nothing."', '"Chance,Political,Support"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"We in Europe must not indulge the illusion that we could shut ourselves away from the world if it goes to pieces, and maybe offer a bit of humanitarian aid."', '"Illusion,World,Europe"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"From my point of view, we have the two communities: the tech community on one side and the rather social-scientific, philosophical community on the other side. We have, from my impression, a disconnect between the two sides."', '"Community,View,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"The question that stands in the foreground is not \'Do we need this technology?\' No one denies the great chances and the great opportunities that we have in the fight against poverty, the handling of climate issues, the fight against sickness."', '"Technology,Great,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"I wish I could say that we Germans have learned from our history once and for all, but I cannot say that when hatred is spreading."', '"History,Wish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', 'Germany\'s historical responsibility will not expire. We want to live up to it - and you should judge us on it.', '"Responsibility,Live,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"We need democracy - but right now democracy needs us! It needs self-assured citizens who have confidence and drive, common sense and decency, and who show solidarity with others."', '"Democracy,Confidence,Drive"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Thirty years ago, this promise, this allure of democracy, drove hundreds of thousands of people in East Germany onto the streets. What courage they showed! It was these brave people, these peaceful heroes and heroines, who brought the Wall tumbling down."', '"Courage,Democracy,Brave"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Following its peaceful reunifica\'tion in 1990, Germany was on track to become an economic giant that had little in the way of foreign policy."', '"Way,Policy,Track"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Since 1998, I have served my country as a member of four cabinets and as the leader of the parliamentary opposition."', '"Country,Opposition,Four"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"But Germany is a reflective power: even as it adapts, a belief in the importance of restraint, deliberation, and peaceful negotiation will continue to guide its interactions with the rest of the world."', '"Power,World,Rest"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6e', '"Germany\'s path to greater military assertiveness has not been linear, and it never will be. Germans do not believe that talking at roundtables solves every problem, but neither do they think that shooting does."', '"Path,Believe,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'To give somebody your time is the biggest gift you can give.', '"Birthday,Time,Gift"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I think working with Johnny Depp was very intimidating. It was my fault though. I mean he\'s a total cool nice, nice guy, but I was just so, I don\'t know, overpowered by his presence. Like he\'s a very mystic person. He\'s older so I never really warmed up around him. I was so stiff."', '"Cool,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'Everybody is great when things are great. It\'s the \'not great\' stuff that matters.', '"Great,Things,Matters"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'When I was a kid at first I wanted to own a candy shop. I guess every kid wants to - we just want to have access - free access.', '"Free,Own,Candy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I\'m so uncomfortable, especially in emotional situations, having to say sentences that don\'t feel right. As an actor - or really, as any kind of person sensitive to it."', '"Feel,Uncomfortable,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I think when I\'m in love, I really am very good with calling, little faxes, and visiting and I really put a lot of effort into it. I\'m really not the one that\'s not available because of work and I\'m very sad when I actually leave."', '"Love,Work,Sad"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'I don\'t like actors who try to talk directors into making their part bigger and that\'s really lame.', '"Talk,Try,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'I was hesitant about doing too big a role in an American movie because it meant losing my German accent.', '"Losing,Doing,American"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I never consciously said, \'I want to be an actor.\' It sounds stupid, but it\'s kind of like being a painter or something. You don\'t say, \'From today on I\'m going to be a painter.\' It\'s not something conscious - you\'ve just been painting pictures all your life."', '"Life,Today,Stupid"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I think I\'m a really good partner and very sensitive to the other person\'s feelings. I want somebody else to be comfortable, to understand about my job, and if they want to come on a set and see me work, they always can."', '"Work,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I said, \'Wouldn\'t it be great if Matt Damon\'s character fell in love with a girl with a real butt?\' They were like, \'Yeah sure, sure - here\'s your personal trainer.\'"', '"Love,Great,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I always performed when I was a child. My parents got very annoyed, because my brother and I had our little bedrooms upstairs, and I would plaster the house with posters with arrows pointing upstairs."', '"Parents,Always,House"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I just want to be able to sit on grass as long as I want to, without anybody telling me to leave. Everything is so restricted, here, in that you actually have to stand behind a line, you can\'t go up the Canyon and enjoy the view."', '"View,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I think there really are a lot of people in the world who probably feel like they\'ve done so much in life, made so much of their talents and ambitions that they feel the need to bequeath it to someone."', '"Life,World,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"People look at me as an exotic person, which is great, because whatever Hollywood is, it seems very dogmatic to me, especially when you\'re a woman. But I always get excused because I\'m German."', '"Great,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I\'ve published one book before, and now I\'m writing a book of essays and stories about life in Tokyo. And I have one book coming out in May in Germany, about fitness."', '"Life,Fitness,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I don\'t really care where I work, actually, because you know making a movie is like living in movie world. There\'s such a secluded world, and the director is the king ruling the country, and everybody\'s building this little town to speak in symbolism."', '"Work,King,World"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'My background is a small town with no movie theater. So... I always pictured myself onstage. I went to acting school and learned all the skills. I left early because I did my first movie and discovered that I really loved the minimalistic work with the camera.', '"Work,Myself,School"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I think actors are divided into two groups: one that wants to be an actor to become famous and rich, and the other that wants to be an actor because they have to be. I\'m more in the second group."', '"Famous,Rich,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I choose my work very carefully, always for the script and the director, and I don\'t think that\'s going to change. My work is like a house. It\'s built on very strong poles."', '"Change,Work,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"When \'Run Lola Run\' came out, the thing about it was it was a very fast-paced film."', '"Film,About,Out"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I like a good, strong statement. I walk out of movies all the time saying, \'That was terrible!\' or \'That sucked!\'"', '"Time,Good,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"When I was told that I was doing a movie called \'Lola Rennt,\' I was like, \'What?\' I didn\'t get it, or the title. I started reading the script, and I still couldn\'t fathom that it was about a person named Lola running. Before my agent explained it to me, I couldn\'t even make any sense out of it."', '"Me,Person,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'We\'ve lost the ability to immerse ourselves in things.', '"Lost,Ability,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I had an American boyfriend, went to football games, tennis tournaments, and to my prom. I was so serious about my American boyfriend that I brought him back to Germany with me to visit my parents. They were horrified."', '"Football,Me,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', 'Don\'t worry about things that haven\'t happened yet.', '"Worry,Things,Happened"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"In most movies, they show you somebody who is perfect looks-wise, and skills-wise, and the movie doesn\'t give you a choice."', '"Movies,Perfect,Choice"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"Everyone thinks \'Lola\' was my first film, but I\'d made 14 movies before that."', '"Movies,Everyone,Film"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I love it when, after a day of shooting, I\'m so exhausted that my bones hurt."', '"Love,Day,Hurt"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I don\'t want to clone anyone, not even myself."', '"Myself,Want,Even"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"The more crazy a person is, the more interesting the person is."', '"Crazy,Person,More"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '\'The Princess and the Warrior\' is looking at the same things as \'Lola\' - just from a different angle.', '"Princess,Looking,Warrior"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I was on \'The Shield,\' which I was a fan of."', '"Fan,Shield,Which"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"As a creative person, you want to be creative, you know? You don\'t want to constantly wait around - a lot of movies fall apart, or there\'s just not as much out there as there used to be."', '"Movies,Wait,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I never wear fur, and I am a spokesperson for PETA."', '"I Am,Never,Wear"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"As an audience, if you see 1800s or something, it more often seems that the actors are carrying the weight of the time. It always has a Shakespearean tone to it. To me, that always feels very theatrical and very unrelatable."', '"Time,Me,See"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"We learn English from fifth grade on in school, and I was an exchange student when I was 17 in Houston."', '"School,Student,Houston"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"What really makes a hero a hero is if you take that person\'s hand, and you walk with that person, and they have a lot of weaknesses, but in the end, they overcome all of their obstacles."', '"Walk,Hero,Obstacles"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I\'ve always hated people in costumes with big heads, where you don\'t know what\'s behind it."', '"People,Know,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe6f', '"I\'ve made movies where I was not happy, and I\'d rather not work for a year than do a bad film. It takes a long time for me to recuperate when I do that."', '"Work,Time,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"Well, we all age, but I\'d been taking herbal supplements for a long time."', '"Time,Age,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"Kids know me from their Grease DVD, so they instantly respond. You can hear a pin drop when I do my old songs."', '"Me,Old Songs,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"When the Beatles came in, I really concentrated on making a lot of movies. Those beach films that we did were a lot fun. They hit with an audience that related to what we were trying to do on the screen. That kept me going all through that Beatle period."', '"Movies,Me,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"Everybody wants instant gratification for everything. It\'s all got to be like fast food. You want a hamburger now, you get it now. Hey, even when McDonald\'s started out, it took them a couple of minutes to make your burger and get it to you. Now, it\'s all wham, bam. That\'s tough enough on a burger. It\'s impossible with a relationship."', '"Relationship,Food,Impossible"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I definitely remember doing \'The Alamo\' with John Wayne and Lawrence Harvey and Linda Cristal. We\'d work six days a week, and then John Wayne would invite us down to a little place in Texas called Del Rio, and we would break bread and have some wine and tell stories."', '"Work,Remember,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'The kids have all seen it on DVD or videotape.', '"Seen,Kids,DVD"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I guess I\'ve maintained my hair. I\'m like a Donald Trump. I have a good, solid head of hair, and that\'s been my trademark all these years."', '"Good,Hair,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I learned not to blink in a close-up or move your head at all, because if you did, they wouldn\'t use it."', '"Your,Close-Up,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I think about growing up back in Philly. It was about friendship with the guys and having a distant crush on some gal. And when you finally got the nerve to take her out on a date, you went to her parents\' house with a shine on your shoes, took her to the movies, and got her home nice and early."', '"Friendship,Home,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I recognize them for what they were. \'DeDe Dinah,\' \'Ginger Bread,\' come on. They\'re fun things. They\'re middle of the road. It wasn\'t really rock and roll. I don\'t know what it was, but it was something accepted and bought, and people still like them. When I reminiscence on stage, people respond. They really like those songs."', '"Fun,Rock And Roll,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I never thought that \'Grease\' would be a smash. I turned it down at first.', '"Never,Down,First"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'When I started to play trumpet I was fortunate to learn very quickly.', '"Play,Fortunate,Trumpet"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'Rocco paid me 35 bucks a week at Murray\'s Inn in South Jersey. People started asking Rocco to have me sing.', '"Me,People,Week"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"No sooner than I did take it seriously, I had million-selling hits and movies with John Wayne."', '"Movies,Seriously,Take"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I was not a trained actor.', '"Actor,Trained"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I\'ll be 65 in September and I work as much as I want to, take cruises with Kay, relax with my family, do everything in moderation, because I want to enjoy my life."', '"Life,Work,Family"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I\'ve been around two years shy of 50 years doing what I do. I am a musician.', '"I Am,Shy,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"They weren\'t great pictures, but they were fun, and they really represented that period of time well."', '"Time,Great,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I think today\'s music absolutely stinks. I really do mean that.', '"Music,Today,Mean"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"These kids today, everything is about hitting a vocal home run."', '"Home,Today,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'They look for the top note to end every song. They don\'t know what they are singing about. There is no style.', '"Look,Style,Song"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"Yes, but I don\'t think of the Teen Angel as of an age."', '"Age,Teen,Angel"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I like that because the fans want to see onstage what they know so well from the big screen.', '"Fans,See,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I wish I could talk to Annette, but she doesn\'t even correspond at this point."', '"Wish,Talk,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'It captures a lot of the spirit of the \'50s.', '"Spirit,Lot,Captures"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '\'Grease\' is the most successful thing I\'ve ever been part of. It spans generations.', '"Successful,Most,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"If I go to a restaurant, or if I\'m at an airport and people recognize me, it amazes me that most of them know me from \'Grease.\'"', '"Restaurant,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I was trying to become a legitimate trumpet player, and I had a scholarship to Eastman School of Music. I was really on my way. But I didn\'t take the scholarship. I got sidetracked, because when summers came around, I started playing with a rock-and-roll band."', '"Music,Way,School"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I studied with Seymour Rosenfeld, who was first trumpeter of the Philadelphia Orchestra."', '"First,Who,Philadelphia"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I love Billy Joel\'s music, but let\'s put it this way - I think this is a frustrated, ugly man."', '"Love,Music,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"If you watch \'American Idol,\' and you close your eyes, you don\'t know who\'s singing because they all sound exactly alike."', '"Eyes,Singing,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I\'m not a chef: I\'m a cook.', '"Chef,Cook"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"The fun of cooking is the fun of communicating with people, even if it\'s just two people. As you\'re cooking, you\'re talking, you\'re having a glass of wine. It\'s wonderful; it\'s an experience. Once you get into cooking, it becomes something that you really look forward to doing."', '"Experience,Cooking,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I still have the tradition of Sunday dinners at my house, and I make all kinds of different Italian foods, and there\'s a lot of fun going on."', '"Fun,Tradition,House"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"I\'ve got eight children, 10 grandkids. I have friends over all the time, and I like to cook."', '"Time,Children,Friends"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"My mother never threw anything out. If there was a sliver of a tomato, it was in the refridge. I would come in with my friends, and Mom would say, \'Want something to eat?\' In 20 minutes, there was four, five dishes to eat."', '"Mom,Never,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"When I was kid, my uncle had a grocery store. I remember the smell of the sawdust on the floor."', '"Remember,Smell,Uncle"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I like to be busy.', '"Busy,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"For me, the biggest successes I\'ve ever had were the ones I never counted on. I never thought my first big record would be a hit. I thought it was an average song."', '"Me,Song,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"It\'s a wonderful thing to be stopped by people, to be recognized, to have somebody come up and say, \'Thank you for all the wonderful memories, for everything... \' Those are compliments you can\'t imagine."', '"Memories,People,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'I eat pasta every day. It gives me energy. I love the taste.', '"Love,Me,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', '"When I was a kid, we\'d go crabbing, as a lot of folks do on the East Coast, and we\'d catch some fresh crabs and take it home, and Mom would turn it into this unbelievable crab gravy - or, as they say, sauce."', '"Home,Mom,They Say"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe70', 'There have been a lot of memorable meals in my life and in my career.', '"Life,My Life,Memorable"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I\'ve never been a morning person, ever. I hate the morning. I have more energy at night."', '"Morning,Hate,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'d like to wrestle an alligator and fly a fighter jet.', '"Fly,Fighter,Alligator"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'There are a lot of country artists now that are heavily influenced by hip-hop. That\'s not me. I was very heavily influenced by rock & roll.', '"Me,Country,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'ve never felt the least bit entitled to airplay. Each spin I get means the world to me.', '"Me,World,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"Someone might look like an overnight success, but there\'s a lot of hard work that goes into it, and rightfully so. That\'s the way it should be. There are exceptions to that rule, but in country music, people really have to pay their dues."', '"Success,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'It\'s amazing how the biggest things in our lives - when we\'re around the fireplace and talking about them when we\'re older - the things that matter the most to us start off amazingly small and in a humble way.', '"Amazing,Humble,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I definitely respect the men and women who came before me and how much those people gave to me musically.', '"Respect,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'m a Detroit Tigers fan through and through.', '"Through,Fan,Detroit"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'Go on stage and stomp my foot on stage and play my guitar and sing my guts out because I love to entertain people. That\'s what makes me happy.', '"Love,Guitar,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I\'ve got an incredible family that I never get to see. I\'ve missed so much. They know how much my career means to me, and they allow me to go and be the workaholic that they never get to see. They support me in that."', '"Family,Me,Support"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"My biggest turn-on is a fine pair of athletic legs. A girl with a fine pair of athletic legs who is not afraid to show them off. Turn-offs? A girl who doesn\'t like country music is a huge turn-off, and girls who don\'t take care of themselves."', '"Music,Care,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"Some people are songwriters, and some people are just recording artists. I\'m both. I write and record."', '"People,Some People,Recording"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I like going to the movies by myself. I love going late at night when there\'s barely anyone in the theater. It\'s very relaxing.', '"Love,Movies,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I want to be the guy with the fresh new sound. I can remember as a kid thinking about a DJ going, \'Ladies and gentlemen, here\'s the new one from Frankie Ballard. He\'s the guy with that hot new sound.\' That\'s the dream."', '"Thinking,Hot,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"Life is relationships and what we\'re trying to do together. And please, that\'s what people have been singing about forever. That\'s what the blues is all about - the good, the bad, the fun, all of it - that lies there in between a man and a woman."', '"Life,Good,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I was born in Battle Creek, Michigan, about 20 miles from Kalamazoo. I lived around there for about seven years. That community is one that I really care about."', '"Community,Battle,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I collect hotel keys. I hope to make something out of them someday. It would be cool to make a bar at my house and, like, the bar is all the hotel keys: lay them down and put glass over them. Or maybe even a coffee table."', '"Cool,Hope,Hotel"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'Money definitely doesn\'t stress me out. I really don\'t care about money... I probably should a little more.', '"Money,Me,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'It really stresses me out to think about what other people think about me.', '"Me,People,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I don\'t really have any hobbies.', '"Hobbies,Really,Any"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"Before you have a hit song, all you\'re doing is banging on the door and screaming, \'I\'ve got something I want to play...\' Now with the hit songs, they\'re like, \'Okay man, we\'re listening. Whaddya got for us?\'"', '"Man,Song,Door"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'m a big \'Cosby Show\' fan.', '"Big,Fan,Show"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I see so many people living in a bubble. They want to be safe, they want their kids to be safe, and they want their friends to be safe. And I get that. That\'s awesome and really admirable. But life is not about who gets out the cleanest at the end, or who\'s the most well-preserved and healthiest."', '"Life,People,Safe"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"The best times I\'ve ever had and the greatest lessons I\'ve ever learned were when my feet were out over the edge of the line, and I was at risk of getting a little beat up, physically and emotionally."', '"Best,Feet,Beat"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I believe it\'s possible to have hit songs and popular music that\'s recorded by human beings.', '"Music,Believe,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I\'ve always expressed myself on guitar, and so I look at it as another voice that is available to say what you need to say."', '"Myself,Guitar,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"\'You\'ll Accomp\'ny Me\' is a song I\'ve always really cherished. The guy in that song is just so courageous. He\'s saying this to the girl, \'I know you\'ve got to go do your thing, but eventually, we\'ll be together. I feel that strong, and I know it in my soul.\' And there\'s something really cool about that."', '"Cool,Together,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I started off as a bar band. We played ZZ Top, Bob Seger, Waylon Jennings, the Rolling Stones - everything and anything people wanted to hear. You\'re not really selling yourself back then; you\'re selling beer."', '"Yourself,People,Beer"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"Are you really into pop? Are you really into old country? Blues? If you\'re not honest about your influences, then things don\'t sound as real as they can be. They\'re not as sharp a cheddar cheese as they can be. And I\'m trying to be the sharpest cheddar I can be."', '"Country,Real,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'ve always been a band guy. That\'s my wheelhouse. That\'s what I do.', '"Always,Band,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'That\'s what music-making is: a dialogue.', 'Dialogue', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'m the world\'s biggest Bob Seger fan. He\'s like my Elvis.', '"World,Fan,He"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"\'Boys of Summer,\' to me, is like the end of the summer, man. That heartbreaking feeling where you have to go back to school, your summer love is coming to an end, and the leaves are changing. That was always such an emotional time for me as a kid, because I loved summer so much."', '"Love,Time,Love Is"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I probably would have never made it through college without baseball, so I\'m thankful for that. I really am proud that I got to play on that level."', '"Thankful,Never,Proud"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"My dad is a big Outlaw country guy - Johnny Cash, Johnny Horton, Waylon, Willie. He loves Elvis and turned me onto Elvis. He was always playing me stuff. He and I would sing and entertain the family. We\'d have a little skit on Thanksgiving or whatever."', '"Family,Dad,Thanksgiving"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'m a huge Travis Tritt fan. I\'m a big Southern rock guy.', '"Big,Rock,Fan"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"It sounds boring, but I\'m such a guitar junkie and a gear junkie. I\'m always fiddling with my stuff. It\'s relaxing to me... I\'m always pulling my stuff apart, getting my pedal board out and fiddling with it or changing guitar strings."', '"Guitar,Me,Boring"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"I\'ve always been a strategy kind of guy. I like laying things out and having a plan. Maybe not always a plan, but an approach and a vibe."', '"Strategy,Always,Plan"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"All my influences go into a pot like a big ole stew, and it tastes like all the years I spent trying to play the guitar like Stevie Ray Vaughn. It tastes like Allman Brothers and Lynyrd Skynyrd. And if it comes out bluesy, then so be it."', '"Guitar,Big,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', 'I\'m always moving like a kid. I\'m always bouncing around and never sit still.', '"Never,Always,Moving"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe71', '"If I\'m blessed enough to have financial freedom in this world, my family is the ones I owe thanks to first."', '"Family,Freedom,World"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I was drinking so much coffee and Red Bull just to keep going it screwed me.', '"Keep Going,Me,Coffee"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I\'ve been studying Israeli army martial arts. I now know 16 ways to kick a Palestinian woman in the back.', '"Woman,Back,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"The Conservative party now exists largely to misinform the public, to convince voters struggling through austerity that they have the same interests as billionaires and corporations."', '"Conservative,Through,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Of course, it\'s absurd that we trust the Tories with our day-to-day reality, as so many of them don\'t really inhabit it. Why elect people to run our schools and hospitals who choose not to go to those schools and hospitals?"', '"Trust,Reality,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"We fear the arrival of immigrants that we have drawn here with the wealth we stole from them. For much of the rest of the world we must be the focus of bitter amusement, characters in a satire we don\'t understand. It is British people that don\'t learn languages, or British history. Britain is the true scrounger, the true criminal."', '"History,Fear,Focus"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I don\'t think I\'m angry. I\'m horrified - powered by horror.', '"Angry,Think,Horror"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'A lot of racism comes from projection. White Americans have a stereotype of black people being criminals purely because they can\'t acknowledge that it was actually white people that stole them from Africa in the first place.', '"Black,People,White"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Creationists have often made me doubt evolution, but probably not in the way they think."', '"Me,Way,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The thing that nobody really said about Rebecca Adlington is that she looks pretty weird. She looks like someone who\'s looking at themselves in the back of a spoon.', '"Looking,Weird,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'In the future we will all be famous for 15 minutes. It will be on a daytime magazine programme and we will each wear a tasteful shirt and slacks combination. We\'ll be interviewed by a soothing voice under a clock that\'s permanently set to 4pm. We will talk about the weather. We will record for months to get 15 minutes they can use in the edit.', '"Future,Famous,Weather"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'To support policies that dehumanise others is to dehumanise yourself.', '"Yourself,Support,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"We live in a culture built on debt, so we are encouraged to have no self control."', '"Culture,Control,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Ed Miliband\'s anti-immigration stance is odd: it\'s hard to vote for a man who doesn\'t have the confidence to defend his own existence.', '"Man,Confidence,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Only the British could experience great pain at the thought of a traffic jam - a place where you can sit alone with your radio on without being expected to do any work. Aren\'t traffic jams unbearable? By the time you get home, you need to sit alone in a comfy chair with your favourite music on just to calm down."', '"Alone,Work,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I love the BBC and I think it\'s a really important thing.', '"Love,Important,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Supporting Rangers, being in an Orange Lodge, that whole life - that\'s a valid culture."', '"Life,Culture,Orange"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"If you\'re an activist trying to do something important, I salute you. Most of us just give ourselves ethical brownie points for watching Channel 2 instead of Channel 3, like characters in a broad dystopian satire."', '"Important,Watching,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I went through a brief phase years ago of getting Men\'s Health then I realised there are actually only three ways to do a sit-up and they\'re just repackaging it endlessly.', '"Health,Men,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"They say that the older you get, the more conservative you become: perhaps that\'s the reason there are no Tories in Scotland."', '"They Say,Conservative,Reason"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'It\'s always easier to dismiss other people than to go through the awkward and time consuming process of understanding them.', '"Time,Process,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Internationally, I propose the radical step of not trying to solve complex political problems with 1,000lb bombs; domestically, I propose they start addressing inequality by paying reparations for slavery. I\'m well aware that in a society where war and discrimination are now almost entirely normalised, both options sound like madness."', '"War,Society,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Doug Stanhope is great - I saw his \'Burning the Bridge to Nowhere\' show and it was inspiring. He\'s like an anti-shaman, taking the sting out of a bunch of things we\'ve chosen to give a symbolic power to. I\'ve made it sound noble and worthy there, it\'s not, it\'s really funny."', '"Funny,Power,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I\'m actually all for political correctness. If you want to work to change the usage of a word that\'s discriminatory then fine, I\'m behind you. But that\'s a conversation that needs to be had in the culture. You can\'t just decide that commonly used parts of a language are evil and that the people who didn\'t get the memo must be bad people."', '"Change,Work,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"For anyone who has ever asked why the U.S. needs to address the issue of reparations for its history of slavery, Donald Trump is why. He is the living embodiment of America\'s unresolved issues."', '"History,America,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I can make a joke pointing out that David Cameron told off Sri Lanka for human rights abuses committed with weapons Britain sold it - like Ronald McDonald calling you a fat bastard.', '"Fat,I Can,Human Rights"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The Conservatives have never been a party burdened by needless sentimentality; some MPs only keep their children\'s photos in their wallet to make sure that at the end of term they don\'t bring the wrong one home.', '"Home,Children,End"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"People think that the Middle East is very complex but I have an analogy that sums it up quite well. If you imagine that Palestine is a big cake, well... that cake is being punched to pieces by a very angry Jew."', '"Angry,Cake,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Of course, it\'s hard to get interested in the whole idea of government. Nothing ever changes, especially people saying \'nothing ever changes,\' despite the fact their kid now has a free nursery place and their aunt was forced to work despite having dementia."', '"Work,Government,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Perhaps we\'ve got so involved in the false selves we project on social media that we\'ve forgotten that our real selves, our private selves, are different, are worth saving."', '"Social Media,Media,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Remember, taboos are just a map of what a society feels it\'s acceptable to be neurotic about. Taboos aren\'t rational."', '"Society,Remember,Map"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"America has gone from the Obama Years to the Trump Years, like going from the \'West Wing\' to a sitcom where the incidental music involves a tuba."', '"Music,America,Gone"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Trump\'s one liberal policy seems to be his desire to pump more funding into mental health - which I\'ve taken the liberty of interpreting as a massive cry for help.', '"Health,Liberty,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The truth is that modern governments sit at the head of a well-funded security apparatus. They are told that foreign military adventures put domestic populations at risk and they give them the thumbs up anyway.', '"Truth,Security,Sit"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Isis want to destroy the knowledge that Islam is a beautiful, scientific and intelligent culture, and we are way ahead of them."', '"Knowledge,Beautiful,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"The SNP are far from radical, but they do have a knack for producing the odd simple, progressive policy that\'s hard to argue against."', '"Simple,Hard,Policy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The average British person would hear me doing my joke about Rebecca Adlington and realise there\'s no malice in it. It was an off-the-cuff ad lib.', '"Me,Person,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Somehow, I always imagine that Trump spends the evenings with his forehead pressed against the cold glass of an aquarium, talking telepathically to the tormented albino squid in which he has hidden his soul."', '"Soul,Glass,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Your ruling class don\'t care about what happens to you. What seems like some enormous upset in your community is undetectable from a helicopter or a speeding motorcade. They are pitiless.', '"Community,Care,Upset"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I\'m totally off any caffeine now.', '"Caffeine,Now,Off"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I have no real enemies in comedy, but there are a couple of people who I\'d laugh about if I heard that their legs had fallen off."', '"People,Laugh,Enemies"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Sectarianism is a real problem, but it should be addressed by people engaging with each other - reconciliation."', '"People,Real,Problem"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"In my early 20s, there was a period when all I owned was about a dozen CDs and a crappy Discman. I\'d listen to \'The Man Who Sold The World\' album endlessly as I sat on off-peak trains jerking around the Sussex countryside to and from the asylum I worked in."', '"Man,World,Countryside"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I loved the idea of Bowie as an artist, with his Burroughsian cut-up technique, creating these undecipherable, abstract songs, where we all projected our own meanings onto his jarring word choices and unexpected chord changes."', '"Unexpected,Choices,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Comedians shame people.', '"People,Shame,Comedians"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I\'ve said jokes where I thought people might get up and hit me for this. A couple of people have thought about it. But they didn\'t. It gives you a lot of power, because if you\'re on shows where people are worried about getting sacked and you\'re not, then you\'re transcendent because you say what other people would like to say."', '"Power,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I read tons of comic books. My favourite is Grant Morrison, a Scottish comic writer."', '"Comic,Books,Read"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I absolutely loathe adverts. I won\'t go into the cinema until 20 minutes after the film is due to start because there are so many.', '"Cinema,Start,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The Internet shows me how limited my interests are - there\'s everything out there and I\'m still looking at what the weather\'s going to be like in Scotland.', '"Weather,Me,Internet"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Comedy is a terrible way to meet women. It\'s certainly a way to start talking to them, but they always have preconceptions about you."', '"Women,Way,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I\'ve never felt any sense of kinship with other comedians; they\'ve always seemed too needy.', '"Never,Always,Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I have some friends who are comedians but not many.', '"Friends,Who,Comedians"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I don\'t believe I\'m a recovering alcoholic - I\'m someone who used to drink. AA comes from a religious movement and that whole thing of \'I\'m always burdened with this\' and the original sin idea. It\'s not like that for me.', '"Me,Believe,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I just want to do something that I feel makes a difference.', '"Feel,Difference,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"British people have a really sophisticated sense of humour, because we\'re exposed to much more than Europeans and Americans, not least in our literary heritage."', '"People,Heritage,More"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I\'m not cynical at all.', 'Cynical', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'That\'s what I do in my stand-up. I work hard and hone the material and after a while audiences expect what I do to be good.', '"Work,Good,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I think the most important things my book does is to give readers the address of George Monbiot\'s website and how to get hold of comic books by Grant Morrison.', '"Website,Important,Comic"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'How hard is it to get female panellists?', '"Hard,Get,How"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I did a ski festival in Austria once. I was struck by how friendly Austrians were, before gradually realising it\'s more that Glaswegians are awful."', '"More,Friendly,Once"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'There\'s still a lot of racism in stand-up.', '"Still,Lot"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Supporting Celtic, waving a tricolour because your parents are Irish - that\'s a valid culture."', '"Culture,Parents,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I think you have a lot of rich and Conservative people who control our country who are racist and their views trickle down through things like tabloid papers.', '"Control,Rich,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"In a lot of farther-flung places in Scotland people are guarded at first, but as soon as they get to know you they really hate you."', '"Hate,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'There are a lot of problems with democracy. We need to think about how to find the people most qualified for the job.', '"Democracy,Problems,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'People feel much more comfortable with the \'Fifty Shades of Grey\' version of women\'s liberation: possibly feeling life would be much simpler if the suffragettes hadn\'t wanted the vote and just really enjoyed chaining themselves to railings.', '"Life,Women,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I think we live in a quite an immoral society with quite an amoral government and they\'re going to have to grow up in that and negotiate their own way in it.', '"Society,Government,Grow"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I worry about everything in this country in particular.', '"Country,Worry,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"The No 1 priority in TV comedy today is \'don\'t frighten the horses,\' and it\'s probably No 2 and 3 as well."', '"Today,Comedy,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I think there is racism at the heart of British policy and has been both in Labour and Conservative times.', '"Heart,Conservative,Policy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'We need to take urgent action on climate change.', '"Change,Action,Climate"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"If I ever get to meet Vladimir Putin, I will probably take my top off and challenge him to an erotically charged wrestling match, which I will let him win."', '"Win,Will,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Corbyn sounds like a dreadful town, dresses like a catalogue model for the Sue Ryder shop and won\'t look significantly different when he\'s been dead for a week."', '"Look,Dead,Week"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'The Tories have been offering us a cocktail of incompetence and malice and Labour haven\'t done anything to draw attention to it. It\'s been like watching Mesut Ozil drop perfect crosses on to the head of an increasingly frustrated Stephen Hawking.', '"Perfect,Done,Watching"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"There\'s been a thread of coverage implying that Corbyn is a decent guy but he clearly doesn\'t understand how the world works. Ignoring the fact that for the majority of people, it doesn\'t."', '"World,People,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"The Labour party has, from the beginning, been made up of diverse factions; that\'s its beauty - asking it to become cohesive is like trying to find one shampoo that will care for the hair of everybody in Angelina Jolie\'s house."', '"Beauty,Care,Hair"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Admittedly, the Conservatives are generally more persuasive orators than their Labour counterparts, perhaps a skill developed by spending school holidays trying to lure father out from behind his Daily Telegraph."', '"Daily,Skill,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"If leadership is about listening, the great political speeches would have been a little different."', '"Leadership,Great,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Let\'s not forget that the essential message of a Republican candidate is a tricky sell. That you love America, but hate all the groups that make up America. That you love democracy, but hate people."', '"Love,Democracy,Hate"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Having our privacy exposed is particularly crushing for the British - a nation for whom the phrase: \'How are you?\' really means: \'Please say one word, then leave me alone.\'"', '"Alone,Me,Privacy"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Consumer culture needs us to be impulsive, while our political culture fears that we will ever develop discipline."', '"Discipline,Political,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"In times of crisis, we are made to feel we should scrutinise our government\'s actions less closely, when surely that\'s when we should pay closest attention."', '"Government,Feel,Attention"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Our attitudes are fostered by a society built on ideas of dominance, where the solution to crises are force and action, rather than reflection and compromise."', '"Society,Reflection,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I\'m not Russell Brand or Ricky Gervais, but I have enough money that I don\'t have to work. Most people who\'ve done what I do don\'t have that."', '"Work,Money,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'I want to be a part of a vibrant culture and have a more open culture.', '"Culture,Open,More"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'People are medicated and TV is one of the things that they are medicated with.', '"People,Things,TV"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'People internalise marketing.', '"People,Marketing"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'People hate jokes.', '"Hate,People,Jokes"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'It is part of my job description to be offensive.', '"Job,Description,Job Description"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"There is no doubt I have offended many people. No doubt, also, that I have blasphemed. I sometimes try to offend as part of my routine - after all, the essence of humour, even in a child, is the effort to shock and surprise."', '"Surprise,Effort,People"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I doubt anyone has ever accused comedians of solidarity before. It\'s hard to think of a less collegiate world than that of unabashed professional narcissists competing for attention; even when we reluctantly band together on panel shows, we\'re only trying to sell solo tours."', '"Together,World,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"On channels terrified of accusations of bias, or political retribution, comics making jokes about the growing power base of far-right politicians aren\'t taking the \'easy\' route."', '"Power,Political,Politicians"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"If you feel more emotion looking at a picture of queuing lorries than a picture of desperate humans living in a lay-by, you need to check your bedtime routine for someone beating you round the head with a meat tenderiser."', '"Looking,Feel,Picture"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"If we can look at another human being and categorise them as \'illegal,\' or that chilling American word \'alien,\' then what has become of our own humanity?"', '"Look,Humanity,Alien"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"There are many indicators of advanced civilisations, but unthinking hero worship of the military isn\'t one of them."', '"Hero,Worship,Military"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"We live in a country where posting \'Let\'s riot or something bruv!\' on Facebook will get you a couple of years in prison, while writing a column saying we should bomb Syria is practically an entrance exam for public intellectuals."', '"Country,Prison,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Bombing Syria will achieve nothing.', '"Nothing,Will,Achieve"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'Islamic State practise a brand of Islamic law so strict that apparently Raqqa only has two Irish Pubs.', '"Law,Two,State"', '2023-05-29 12:03:00', '2023-05-29 12:03:00'),
	('399344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"I think we live in a country that sometimes forgets how effective the rule of law is, perhaps because our governments have often found it inconvenient."', '"Law,Country,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', '"Trump divides his time between working some kind of \'King Ralph\' angle, and claiming that he\'s going to make the U.S. great again by using his business experience. We can only assume that means repeatedly declaring it bankrupt, then changing its name so he can just shake off all the debt."', '"Experience,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe72', 'You can actually make your own Trump policies by going through the incinerator at the Daily Mail and picking through the dust for anything they thought might get them prosecuted.', '"Daily,Own,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"The thing is, I feel like it would defeat the purpose of being a musician if I let any kind of fear of failure affect my songwriting or making an album or whatever."', '"Failure,Fear,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I think I\'d like my hair to be perfect.', '"Perfect,Hair,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I kind of like the idea of creating my own literature within my albums. I definitely thought about that when I started writing songs.', '"Literature,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I can be very social, but often, it weighs down on me later that the social thing was a put-on. I feel like my way of dealing with not wanting to go out is, I just don\'t. I can\'t bring myself to."', '"Myself,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I\'m not just going to hug every person that asks to hug me.', '"Me,Hug,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I don\'t really understand how to do bureaucratic things - school-system things.', '"Understand,Things,How"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I never was interested in acting, and I never became good at it."', '"Good,Acting,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I love going to weddings. I love movie scenes of weddings. Even, like, TV-show weddings - I cry at every wedding."', '"Love,Wedding,Cry"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I meet a lot of people after shows, and I have to say it\'s pretty intense."', '"People,Meet,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I knew that \'Next Thing\' was an angry album while I was making it. But I thought that it was angry the way that you get in a fight, not angry as a huge life change."', '"Life,Change,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"If I could have a record that represents every stage of my life, I\'d be putting out one a month. Everything is always changing, and so is the way that I feel about stuff."', '"Life,My Life,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'It\'s funny: \'Next Thing\' was written in a time of my life when I was actually really naive and thought that I was wise.', '"Life,Funny,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"The first music-learning thing that I took seriously was piano lessons when I was a kid. I guess that was probably the only time that I was forced to perform music, because I had piano recitals, and my school also had mandatory music classes that had some performing required."', '"Time,Music,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Performing is something that has really grown on me and become an important part of my life, which I didn\'t used to feel. I didn\'t used to want to really perform live a lot. It\'s been an interesting adjustment."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Sometimes I\'ll write something that\'s purely autobiographical, and sometimes pure fiction, and sometimes a mix."', '"Sometimes,Pure,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I think that I\'m definitely going to keep writing music forever. I can\'t stop even if I tried.', '"Music,Forever,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I really liked punk music and experimental music that my brother was taking me to go see in the city, when I was probably, like, 13 years old. I was seeing a lot of teenagers making \'weird\' music, and I think that was probably a big part of the reason that I actually started to play myself."', '"Music,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"It was a really long process, dropping out of college. I was there for a semester, then I would take a semester off and go on tour, then I would go back for a semester."', '"Long,Process,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I\'m always the one sitting at the merch table and talking to everyone at the show - and I think it\'s because I have this deep fear that if I\'m not approachable or I\'m not there, people are going to think I\'m a brat."', '"Fear,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I definitely think that touring is a really crazy lifestyle and makes it hard to live a normal life and have relationships and friendships.', '"Life,Crazy,Lifestyle"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"What I really care about is writing... Some people feel about touring the way I feel about writing, which is, \'Whoa, I can\'t believe I get to do this as a job.\'"', '"Believe,Care,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I was seeing kids my age playing shows at their parents\' houses or the couple of all-ages venues that existed. I feel like I saw so many different kinds of music that I wouldn\'t have discovered on my own.', '"Age,Music,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"My brother was 13 when people started telling me that he was a \'hipster.\' I was 11 and thought it was so stressful, like, \'How do you not be called that?\'"', '"Me,People,Brother"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"My parents listened to a lot of James Taylor and Hall and Oates. My mom and I used to listen to Liz Phair and Indigo Girls a lot in the car, too."', '"Car,Mom,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Around seventh grade, I got a guitar and forgot everything else."', '"Guitar,Everything,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"You meet a lot of people in New York who are different than you and have different stories, so I see everyone as super individual. I feel like I can be infinitely inspired because New York is huge."', '"Feel,New,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I realized I was trained my whole life to be an accommodating person, to make sure that everybody is comfortable before I\'m comfortable. After giving so much of myself to strangers, I learned to care for myself a little more, especially on tour."', '"Life,Myself,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I don\'t actually have problems dealing with corporate situations. There are times I\'ve railed against it, but there are other times when I\'m like, \'I\'ll take your money, no problem.\'"', '"Money,Problems,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"If I had to pick an artist that I look up to and am inspired by, it\'s Matisse because of how many times he would paint the same idea until he felt like he maybe got it right, and I try to do the same thing with my writing."', '"Look,Right,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I think part of the process of putting out a record is always looking back because, by the time a song comes out, it\'s been a year since you wrote it."', '"Time,Looking Back,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Once you\'re in a position where you can choose to not be around toxic environments, just do that as much as you can."', '"Position,Choose,Once"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"It\'s good for people to be able to see an archive of an artist learning how to write and getting better, especially for teenagers who are starting to write: to see that I started out making pretty easy and weird and bad-sounding music and that you can teach yourself how to write over a long period of time."', '"Time,Good,Learning"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"My parents have both done some music stuff. My family was very artist-friendly, so that was encouraging."', '"Family,Music,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"When I was 16, I really decided that music was something I wanted to do."', '"Music,Something,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Those emotions that are really strong, the ones that inspire a song, you can hold onto that. You can let it marinate for years and keep writing about it even better than you did then."', '"Emotions,Song,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'It\'s even easier to write about the past now that I\'m happy and have better stuff to write about. That\'s why someone like Bob Dylan can make so many records over so long a time; it\'s not like he\'s been sad all this time. He\'s really successful!', '"Sad,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I go through phases sometimes: \'I\'m a genius; they get me,\' and sometimes I\'m like, \'Why does anyone want to hear me?\'"', '"Me,Genius,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"The way my body is viewed in the world is different than a male body. People are going to write about the performance, but they\'re probably also going to be writing about what I was wearing or my hair, which just doesn\'t happen to men."', '"Men,World,Hair"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I try to not assume things are sexism. I\'m trying to be good natured about why things are happening.', '"Good,Trying,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'The only reason to do this job is because I love playing my music. And I love my bandmates.', '"Love,Music,Job"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I don\'t even know how people managed without the Internet years ago. Having to mail a cassette tape of your music to strangers over the course of months... I just can\'t imagine having to do that.', '"Music,Internet,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"When I was 18, I borrowed my parents\' car, and they are super supportive. They might give us snacks for the road, but it\'s not like they are paying clubs to book us."', '"Car,Parents,Road"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I feel like I can\'t write something that has a real emotion in it if I can\'t connect to that emotion.', '"Feel,Real,Connect"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"There\'ve been times on tour when people have said to us, \'Yeah, your band is really simple.\' But it\'s really not."', '"Simple,People,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'Sometimes I\'m really mean to someone who just hugged me. I never thought that I would be like that.', '"Me,Sometimes,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I\'ve definitely gotten to the point where we get to the venue, and people know that I\'m in charge of the band."', '"People,Know,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'I think I\'m always changing as a writer and trying new things.', '"New,Trying,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I played my first show when I was 17, and that was a big moment. I realized it was something I could keep doing."', '"Moment,Doing,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I feel like touring is a man\'s game. And I don\'t think that\'s sexist; I just think, on tour, you can\'t really take care of yourself the way you want to."', '"Man,Game,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"If I ever go back to college, I\'d study art education."', '"Education,Art,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', 'One of the cool things about traveling and being a musician is that you meet so many people who have studied different things and have different careers.', '"Cool,People,Meet"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"I\'ve played Frankie Cosmos shows where the promoter or whoever sees that I\'m the lead singer, and then they go up to David, the bassist, and are like, \'So, do we pay you?\' And he\'s like, \'No, you pay her; she\'s the boss.\' Those are moments where I\'m just like, \'I\'m clearly in charge.\'"', '"Boss,Cosmos,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"My Bandcamp had a lot of bad and good music, but I relied on that to sort my feelings. My sadness will always be there, even in the happiness."', '"Happiness,Good,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe73', '"Whenever I\'m really excited about a song, I want to learn it, and it becomes the first thing I play every time I pick up an instrument."', '"Time,Song,Excited"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I\'m into a lot of music, definitely a lot of rap. \'Dedication 4\', the Lil\' Wayne album. Actually, I\'ve been getting into some Swedish house music; the beat just keeps me going a little bit."', '"Music,Me,Dedication"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I feel like I\'m still improving, still getting better, and I have a lot more to give in this sport."', '"Better,Feel,Getting Better"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I always tell people, \'The week after your fight is just a very good time.\' You get to release, relax, unwind mentally - everything."', '"Time,Good,Relax"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I coach at Rutgers University and help out there as a part-time assistant coach. I feel like the coach is kind of in me, and it would also be great exposure, so I\'d be down for it, for sure."', '"Great,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"Best memories - obviously, winning a title for the first time. Probably my last fight against Gray Maynard where I was able to finish him for the trilogy. Those were definitely great moments. The worst moments are the losses, for sure."', '"Best,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I get a lot of attention, maybe not as much as a lightweight in B.J. Penn or someone like that, but my time is coming."', '"Time,Attention,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I got two young kids, so as much as I train a lot, free time is spent with my kids."', '"Time,Free,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"You learn a lot as a coach when you sit back and tell someone what to do, and then you realize, \'Hey, I need to start doing that myself.\' I think coaching can improve a fighter\'s game tremendously."', '"Myself,Game,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"Best matchup? You know, I don\'t really know. It doesn\'t really matter, and whoever has the belt would be fine for me."', '"Best,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I believe a lot of techniques and stuff has to do with confidence, and I think as my confidence grows, everything else will grow as well."', '"Confidence,Believe,Grow"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"Everybody says they\'re going to knock me out, and no one\'s done it yet."', '"Me,Done,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', 'There\'s nothing like going to real live UFC events. It\'s unbelievable.', '"Nothing,Live,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"We\'re not getting judged or rated by just our fighting ability. People want to watch guys who are flamboyant and have something to say, and that\'s just the nature of the fight game and the game we\'re in. I get it."', '"Nature,Fight,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I need a little more \'Jersey Shore\' in me, I guess. It\'s just not who I am. It would almost be phony at this point."', '"Me,I Am,More"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', 'I\'m still here. I\'m still gunning for that title. I\'m not going anywhere.', '"Title,Here,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"Nothing comes easy. I\'m OK with that. If I think I\'m the best guy, I should be able to beat anybody."', '"Best,Nothing,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I don\'t know if you want to call it, like, \'an old school guy\' or what, but you\'ve got to go out there; you\'ve got to perform in order to get what you want. I\'m willing to put my skills on the line and put my heart on the line just to say I\'m the best and prove that I can achieve this title."', '"Best,Heart,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"You always have to play it safe, no matter who you\'re fighting. I don\'t fight any easy guys. I haven\'t maybe ever in the UFC. To me, you\'ve always got to be safe. But I don\'t want to have my foot on the brake at all. My foot is going to be on the gas, and I\'m going to be smart at everything."', '"Fight,Me,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"I never picked fights. I\'m never going to start to pick fights. If they ask me to fight someone, I\'ll say yes."', '"Fight,Me,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe74', '"Let\'s be real: it\'s not always the No. 1 contenders who get the title shots. It\'s who they invest money in and who\'s kind of a known name. In the lighter weights, just being that I fought seven title fights in a row, I think I\'m that guy."', '"Money,Real,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', 'No one deserves any more respect than the other person until they prove themselves unworthy.', '"Respect,Person,Prove"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"Respect is such a simple and easy thing to have and to give, and it doesn\'t cost anything."', '"Respect,Simple,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"Your time here on this earth, it belongs to you."', '"Time,Earth,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', 'I think it is so important to pass down knowledge and information to younger generations.', '"Knowledge,Information,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"When you look in the mirror at the end of the day, make sure you feel good about what you see."', '"Good,Mirror,Feel Good"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"Don\'t be afraid to see the gift and talent you have, because that thing could lead to a substantial career for you. Because we all do something as good or better than most people."', '"Good,Gift,Talent"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"I love Montclair. I loved it; it was great for my kids. I raised them all there, brought them up through the Montclair school system, and two of my daughters went to Montclair State."', '"Love,Great,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"Far too often, I have been accepted or rejected for work because of the color of my skin."', '"Work,Skin,Far"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', '"I\'ve been asked far too often, \'Can you be blacker?\' I\'ve gotten done with auditions and heard, \'We\'re not going to go black with this character.\'"', '"Black,Character,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe75', 'I don\'t do things by the book.', '"Things,Book"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I was Boots The Monkey in \'Dora The Explorer Live Dora\'s Pirate Adventure,\' and it was the greatest!"', '"Monkey,Live,Adventure"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'The best part of social media is that you can reach a lot of people. But that\'s also the worst part of social media.', '"Best,Social Media,Media"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Anything that has a dragon, a wand, pixie dust, fairies, magic, any of that, I love it. I\'m obsessed with it, I will read it, I will watch it, I will commit it to memory."', '"Love,Memory,Fairies"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"If you happen to be in an environment where people are not accepting of who you are, you just need to know that\'s not always the way it will be."', '"Way,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Having this message of sobriety and recovery to blast out into the world is also very powerful and kind of the reason why I\'m on this planet, I think; it\'s one of my purposes."', '"World,Why,Reason"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Opening presents at midnight on Christmas Eve - midnight! As soon as it turns to Christmas Day, we\'re opening those gifts."', '"Christmas,Day,Opening"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I basically raised her. Ariana and I are 10 years apart, and she grew up with a really gay brother who just loves her unconditionally, and it\'s reciprocated."', '"Gay,She,Brother"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Be true to yourself, no matter what that is."', '"Yourself,True,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'The party life that had once given me so much confidence and comfort had turned into a nightmare where I never felt more alone.', '"Life,Alone,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"OMG, I have my \'Mamma Mia!\' playbill framed in my bedroom. It was magical! I totally cried... a lot! I remember collecting playbills my entire life, and then to be in one... I have no words."', '"Life,Words,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I like singing Bruce Springsteen.', '"Singing,Like,Bruce Springsteen"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I have a major weakness for Oreo cookies and David Yurman jewelry.', '"Cookies,Jewelry,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I love being back on the East Coast.', '"Love,Back,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I got the first Nintendo system, and me and my mother would stay up and play it together for hours and hours and hours - mainly Super Mario Brothers and Mario Kart!"', '"Together,Me,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"After the tragic events of Manchester, with the senseless loss of life and the fear that came from knowing my family was unsafe and that I was completely powerless to protect them, I went to a very dark place with no tools to handle the feelings that came along with the devastation of the attack."', '"Life,Family,Fear"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I am here today as an example to all that have gone through a personal hell or are going through it right now, whatever that hell might be for you, that you can become whole again. In fact, you can become stronger than you ever thought possible."', '"Today,Hell,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I am a new man, and the man you see before you is the one I was always meant to be. This decision to be sober is a lifetime decision."', '"Man,Decision,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"My mom. My grandma, my grandfather. We have a very strong, strong line of amazing people in the family. Very strong women."', '"Family,Women,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"My mother is a rock. She\'s my rock, she\'s Ariana\'s rock, and she has been a huge example of how to get through some difficult situations with strength, dignity, her head held high."', '"Strength,Difficult,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I can pretty much name and rattle off the genus and species of all the bugs you see in everyday life.', '"Life,See,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I remember being so nervous to tell my little sister. I was like, \'I have something to tell you... I\'m gay.\' And she was like, \'Cool, do you have a boyfriend?\' And I was like, \'Yeah,\' and she was like, \'When do I get to meet him?\' I was, like, \'Really? It\'s that simple?\' So it went really well."', '"Cool,Simple,Gay"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'There\'s a lot of audience participation in \'Rock of Ages\' and \'Rocky Horror.\'', '"Rock,Audience,Participation"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I love breaking the fourth wall, and being given permission to play with the audience!"', '"Love,Audience,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'It\'s difficult to market and promote a new show that no one has heard of with a not unique title.', '"Difficult,New,Unique"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"\'Ray of Light\' changed my life. The whole album, but that song specifically, was just so life-changing and incredible for me."', '"Life,Me,Light"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I love Muhlenberg. I\'m an academic. I needed a small school with incredible programs and found that here. I learned so much and grew so much in four years.', '"Love,School,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Muhlenberg is the school that made me and shaped me into the actor I am today.', '"Today,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'There\'s nothing like the spontaneity of making something work on stage.', '"Work,Nothing,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I\'m extremely excited about returning to my alma mater, working with my amazing professors and being part of Muhlenberg Theatre & Dance once again. I believe the program to be the absolute best in the nation!"', '"Best,Amazing,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'My first audition ever was for \'Bye Bye Birdie\' in fifth grade.', '"First,Audition,Ever"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I have the most incredible fans, and they have given me so many wonderful gifts. My apartment is decorated almost entirely with fan art."', '"Art,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"You can see things growing up, be inspired by things. Just because they\'re not around anymore doesn\'t mean that you can\'t take those inspirations and bring them to life and bring them to the next generation."', '"Life,Generation,See"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'David Bowie has always been my vocal inspiration ever since I was a child.', '"Always,Inspiration,Child"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I definitely take influences from my idols David Bowie and Billy Joel. I\'ve combined them with the Frankie Grande-isms that I\'ve cultivated over singing every night for two shows a week for four years on Broadway.', '"Night,Singing,Idols"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Glam rock always has a story to tell and has that powerful voice with a little hint of libretto.', '"Voice,Always,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"As long as you adore my sister, then you\'re O.K. by me."', '"Me,Long,Sister"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I was in love with Ryan Phillippe. I mean, like, who wasn\'t?"', '"Love,Mean,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I\'m really embracing that very out, very loud, very free persona that I am now but that I didn\'t get to be in high school."', '"I Am,Free,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I love working in TV. And I love the adrenaline of hosting things like \'Access Hollywood\' with, like, zero preparation and just going straight on."', '"Love,Preparation,Adrenaline"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I want people to be obsessed with Broadway and theatre as much as I am.', '"I Am,People,Theatre"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I love my Justin Bieber. He\'s, like, my favorite person of all time, so I\'m always looking through his social media posts."', '"Love,Time,Social Media"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I am emoji-heavy as hell. I\'d use the same emoji 140 times just to communicate how excited I am.', '"Hell,I Am,Excited"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Your Instagram shouldn\'t have 35 pictures from the same event.', '"Your,Same,Pictures"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"You don\'t have to post a picture with every single person at the party. Just get a few, maybe post one picture with eight people."', '"Picture,People,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'There\'s always a performance going on in our house.', '"Performance,Always,House"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Ariana is anything but subtle.', '"Anything,Subtle"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I was pre-med in college, and so since a lot of people take a year off before they go to med school, I decided to take the time to pursue theater - six months later, I was on Broadway."', '"Time,People,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I have to say, Franz in \'Rock of Ages,\' I had three final callbacks for that role before I booked it - it was something that I\'d dreamed of. I wanted to play that role. I love that show."', '"Love,Three,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I\'m obsessed with Maggie Smith - the way that she can be the most brilliant actress in every single situation and then do Harry Potter, and still make me cry while she\'s casting spells with a wand?"', '"Me,Way,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Madonna is my absolute queen - as a performer, there\'s no one better than her."', '"Queen,Better,Her"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I think operating in a mode of fear, and operating from a mode of fear, is not going to get us anywhere, as a people, or me, as a person. So I don\'t operate from that place."', '"Fear,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I try very hard to live my life in an exemplary way, which is, you know, \'Shine bright like Frankie.\'"', '"Life,My Life,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Broadway performers are the best-trained people on the planet.', '"People,Planet,Broadway"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Every day of my life, I wish I was on Broadway. It\'s my favorite place. It\'s my heart; it\'s my soul."', '"Life,Heart,Soul"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"I showed my nana, who lives in Delray, my writeup in the \'New York Times,\' and she said, \'When will you be in the \'Sun Sentinel?\'"', '"Sun,New,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"No one wants to follow someone fake or boring. Being accessible on social media, being honest, and having fun with it is key."', '"Social Media,Fun,Boring"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'Instagram really gives me a chance to be creative.', '"Chance,Me,Creative"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', '"Women who have been with man after man after man after man choose to become a lesbian later in life. Gay men, it doesn\'t work so much that way."', '"Life,Work,Women"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I have at least four Starbucks drinks a day.', '"Day,Four,Starbucks"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'I know all the words to Billy Joel\'s \'We Didn\'t Start the Fire.\'', '"Fire,Words,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'My favorite vacation destination is Hawaii.', '"Destination,Vacation,Hawaii"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe76', 'My sister\'s Ariana Grande.', 'Sister', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', '"My grandma was actually a pretty well-known opera singer in Cuba, and then my mom was a ballerina. Two of my three sisters are dancers, so we grew up in the arts."', '"Mom,Three,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', '"When you\'re auditioning for commercials, they\'re looking for a Latin guy in his 20s, and you\'ll show up, and it\'s a bunch of people who look just like you, and it\'s a little weird. More often than not, they\'re way better-looking. They\'re taller. They have way more abs than you do."', '"Look,Looking,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', '"I can\'t point to my work and say, \'This is my work.\' My work lives in me, so when people criticize my work, they\'re also criticizing me. It\'s really hard to sort of divorce that sensitivity."', '"Work,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', '"You put a lot of yourself into a character, so even though he\'s not you, in a sense it is you."', '"Character,Yourself,He"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', 'One of my first jobs was doing children\'s theater. I did it to get my union card.', '"Children,Doing,First"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe77', '"My dad was very religious growing up and a little bit closed minded, and I think me being in the theater, two of my three sisters are dancers, so being in the arts world has changed and opened him up in a lot of ways."', '"Dad,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"I am keeping with tradition today. After I learned of my Golden Globe nomination, I went to the dentist, so today, let\'s make it the orthodontist."', '"Today,I Am,Golden"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', 'I know I am no better than anyone else in this world.', '"World,I Am,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"Yeah, I like cars and basketball. But you know what I like more? Bananas."', '"Know,More,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"Acting classes, I guess, are good and I would like to maybe sometime take one. But I would feel like I was learning someone else\'s technique. I like mine."', '"Good,Learning,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"Some kids are always getting into trouble or doing stuff, and I stay away from those types. I know I am no better than anyone else in this world. I\'m just an actor, that\'s nothing special. But I\'m not into anything bad. Just blackjack."', '"World,I Am,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"I wanna do movies that in ten years time people will respect me for, as an actor. So if I do take two years off or three years off, the next movie I have that comes out you want people to go \'ooh, that\'s Frankie Muniz\'s new movie, it\'s gonna be a good movie cause he\'s in it.\'"', '"Respect,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"There was a scene cut out of \'Big Fat Liar\' (2002) where I had to wear a dress. This may sound kind of weird, but I really enjoyed shooting that scene."', '"Liar,Dress,Fat"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe78', '"I\'m just an actor, that\'s nothing special."', '"Nothing,Special,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', 'I am fully a feminist in this modern definition of the term. It\'s innate in my work because that\'s just who I am.', '"Work,I Am,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"When I first had Isaac, I only owned a mattress. Now I have a show?"', '"First,Now,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"I discovered that my biggest passion was for directing, so in making opportunity for myself, I found what I like doing the best."', '"Best,Myself,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"I moved out to L.A. and had my son and was walking around Gelson\'s, and I was like, \'Am I just one giant, lactating boob? Is that what I\'ve become?\'"', '"Walking,Son,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"There was a feeling I had when I got pregnant and decided to keep the baby, and I knew I wasn\'t going to be with the baby daddy, and I was really toying with what my identity would be."', '"Identity,Baby,Feeling"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"There\'s this idea that motherhood is as American as apple pie, but yet we don\'t support it with any government assistance."', '"Government,Support,American"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', 'I want to disappear in a role.', '"Disappear,Want,Role"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"Most of the stories I write are women\'s stories - but the darker, unseen stories."', '"Women,Unseen,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"When my son was small, he just came with me everywhere, whether it was going to yoga class or auditions or sleeping over at friends\' houses. We came as a pair."', '"Me,Son,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"We had no money. My family was in Southie; I was in affluent Brookline. I don\'t know if it\'s my personality or the circumstance, but it all kind of led to this feeling of being an observer on the outside."', '"Family,Money,Personality"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"Because I\'d grown up with this singular focus on sports, I just kind of did that with acting. That became an obsession. How am I going to make it? How am I going to figure that out?"', '"Sports,Focus,Acting"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"I moved to L.A. because I didn\'t want to be in New York anymore. And I knew if I wanted to act, it would have to be in one of those places."', '"New,Act,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe79', '"I was actually really sick of being a broke actress with a toddler, so I wrote a script."', '"Sick,Actress,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'You can take the guy out of the neighorhood but you can\'t take the neighborhood out of the guy.', '"Neighborhood,Guy,Take"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"One day, when I was still living at home, a friend told \'Texas\' Jean Valli about me. She was originally from Syracuse, N.Y., and lived in New Jersey but sang country. One night, she had me come up on stage where she was performing. I sang \'My Mother\'s Eyes,\' and she was knocked out."', '"Home,Eyes,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I cherish the memory of being a friend of Frank Sinatra on a friendship level to the point where we really hung out. We worked in Vegas, we\'d talk on the phone, and if I wasn\'t doing anything, I\'d fly out, and I spent time in Palm Springs at his house - on a level the way friends would be, not with a whole crowd of people."', '"Friendship,Time,Fly"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"When I was a kid, I used to listen to my Emerson radio late at night under the covers. I started by listening to jazz in the late 1940s and then vocal harmony groups like the Four Freshmen, the Modernaires and the Hi-Lo\'s. I loved Stan Kenton\'s big band - with those dark chords and musicians who could swing cool with individual sounds."', '"Cool,Night,Harmony"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"Where I grew up, in New Jersey, there was a lot of organised crime activity. It was a part of life."', '"Life,New,Activity"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'Jazz was my first love.', '"Love,Jazz,First"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"Starting in my teens, I was always standing on the corner near our apartment singing harmony with friends. We\'d also go to the park and sing under the bridge near the lake for the echo. When it was cold out, we\'d stand in the little heated lobby in the project\'s administration building, where my mom paid the rent each month."', '"Mom,Bridge,Singing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I\'d seen so many people become stagnant in New Jersey - I had this fear I\'d just stay there. They\'d come out of high school, get a job, get married, have kids and die in Jersey. I wanted more."', '"Fear,Die,New"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"The \'60s was a magical time in the music business. So much creativity and talent. I think a lot of it came from the fact that we had grown up before rock n\' roll. We listened to all the great songwriters and big bands, songs with great lyrics and melodies. I think that really influenced everybody."', '"Business,Time,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I always believed a singer should be able to sing any kind of song. If I wanted to sing a Cole Porter song, I should be able to do that. Or \'Sherry,\' I should be able to do that. Or a Dylan song."', '"Song,Always,Able"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I went to school to learn to be a hairdresser. I worked at a wholesale florist, where I delivered to florists all over New Jersey. I\'d come home and go out to work down at the Shore. The early jobs, I remember, were $5, $6 a night. And I lived in the projects right until the time I became successful."', '"Work,Time,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"With \'Sherry,\' we were looking for a sound. We wanted to make the kind of mark that, if the radio was playing one of our songs, you knew who it was immediately. But I didn\'t want to sing like that my whole life."', '"Life,Looking,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"At school, I\'d sing in groups in the locker room or in the bathroom, which was like an echo chamber. The problem is I didn\'t know how to get started singing professionally. The pool hall was my Facebook. I\'d hang out there to keep up with what was going on and to let people know where I could be reached if singing jobs came up."', '"Singing,People,School"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'I\'m not doing contemporary songs unless something comes along that really knocks my socks off.', '"Doing,Something,Socks"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I spent many a summer early morning with the radio very low, half sleeping and half listening."', '"Morning,Summer,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"It was very important to establish a sound, so that people heard a record on the radio and knew immediately that it was you."', '"People,Important,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'I do belong to Jersey. There\'s no doubt about that in my mind. They have been so loyal and so good to me; how could I possibly belong any place else?', '"Good,Me,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I grew up beyond proud - we didn\'t have much, but we had a lot of love."', '"Love,Proud,Beyond"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"When we were trying to get \'Jersey Boys\' off the ground, I\'d get, \'The Four Seasons? Who\'s going to care? There\'s the Beatles, there\'s the Rolling Stones.\' But people know those stories. Here was a story no one knew."', '"Care,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I learned by listening to other people sing and doing impressions of them. And there are things no one can ever teach you, like phrasing. By listening to Sinatra, for instance - you felt that everything he sang had happened in his life."', '"Life,People,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"In 1967, I found out I was losing my hearing. I went 10 years without any help. I had otosclerosis - hardening of the bone in the middle of the ear."', '"Losing,Help,Bone"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"Becoming successful is a relentless pursuit. It\'s good that it\'s that way: When it does come, you learn to know how to appreciate it, and know how lucky you are to be doing something that you love so much."', '"Love,Good,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"If I close my eyes, I can remember the first apartment where I lived with my family in Newark, N.J., in the late 1930s. The rooms were lined up like train cars - you had to go through one to get to another - and there wasn\'t any heat or hot water."', '"Family,Eyes,Water"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'People don\'t get married to get divorced. Maybe people weren\'t meant to be together forever.', '"Together,People,Meant To Be"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'It\'s unconditional love with your kids.', '"Love,Unconditional Love,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I don\'t play golf or tennis, I don\'t ski, I don\'t snowboard. If you love what you do, you never get enough of it."', '"Love,Never,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', 'My name actually is Francesco Castaluccio.', '"Name,Actually"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I thought everybody had falsetto. And since I wasn\'t a schooled singer who studied with anybody, I just thought anybody who had a voice could do anything they wanted with their voice."', '"Voice,Anything,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"Establishing a style is important, it really is, but a lot of singers get so involved with their instrument, and more so than they do in what they\'re singing. I think you really have to think about what you\'re singing. You have to make the public believe what you\'re singing. And in order to do that, you have to believe it."', '"Believe,Style,Singing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"The very first time I ever heard anything of mine on the radio, I was in New Jersey, and I was in my teens. I did my first record, which was an old standard called \'My Mother\'s Eyes.\' It was the old Georgie Jessel theme. I heard it on local radio out of Newark. And it was very exciting!"', '"Time,Eyes,New"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"There were a lot of R&B groups that were my heroes, but the funny thing about my career and the way it went and where it went, at first I didn\'t really want to do pop music. I was a little bit more into jazz and R&B."', '"Funny,Music,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I think Lady Gaga is talented. Madonna is talented, and the flair that Michael Jackson had. He was talented! Whatever it is that they do, they must be doing something right. They do have an audience out there, so I respect that."', '"Respect,Lady,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"I have to believe that most people know that \'Can\'t Take My Eyes Off Of You\' is my song. But the reaction we get from the audience at \'Jersey Boys\' is that they didn\'t remember how many hits we had. A lot of \'Oh yeah, I forgot they did that song.\' We had 20 Top 10 hits in the U.S... people forget."', '"Eyes,Believe,Song"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '\'Jersey Boys\' has been the most amazing experience ever and has exposed an entire new audience to the music. It\'s great to see people of all ages coming to the show.', '"Experience,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"It\'s always very special for me to work Chicago. Both of the record companies I was with, early on, were based in Chicago. The music was always huge there."', '"Work,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7a', '"When somebody is making a movie about your life, that\'s different. A show is a live performance. Things are going to go wrong. You are going to get away with things. A movie is indelible. A movie is through a microscope."', '"Life,Live,Performance"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"I auditioned for Roosevelt in \'The Winds of War,\' but Ralph Bellamy got the role."', '"War,Role,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"When you talk about a character on a situation comedy, it\'s not just the actor. It\'s the writers, too."', '"Character,Situation,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"Everything I\'ve done until \'The Jeffersons\' - the plays, the movies, the soap operas - were all in New York."', '"Movies,New,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"I got to work with Ingrid Bergman, and it was a wonderful experience."', '"Work,Experience,Wonderful"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"When a show is popular, sometimes the industry dismisses it."', '"Sometimes,Industry,Show"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7b', '"When I go to New York, all the skycaps want my autograph."', '"New,Go,Autograph"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"When you reach the end of your rope, tie a knot in it and hang on."', '"Motivational,End,Rope"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"We have always held to the hope, the belief, the conviction that there is a better life, a better world, beyond the horizon."', '"Life,Hope,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"In politics, nothing happens by accident. If it happens, you can bet it was planned that way."', '"Politics,Way,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The only thing we have to fear is fear itself.', '"Fear,Only,The Only Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"If civilization is to survive, we must cultivate the science of human relationships - the ability of all peoples, of all kinds, to live together, in the same world at peace."', '"Science,Peace,Relationship"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Let us never forget that government is ourselves and not an alien power over us. The ultimate rulers of our democracy are not a President and senators and congressmen and government officials, but the voters of this country."', '"Power,Government,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Democracy cannot succeed unless those who express their choice are prepared to choose wisely. The real safeguard of democracy, therefore, is education."', '"Education,Democracy,Choice"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'I ask you to judge me by the enemies I have made.', '"Me,Enemies,Judge Me"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Take a method and try it. If it fails, admit it frankly, and try another. But by all means, try something."', '"Try,Something,Take"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The test of our progress is not whether we add more to the abundance of those who have much it is whether we provide enough for those who have little.', '"History,Progress,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'There are as many opinions as there are experts.', '"Opinions,Many,Experts"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Happiness lies in the joy of achievement and the thrill of creative effort.', '"Happiness,Success,Achievement"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"A conservative is a man with two perfectly good legs who, however, has never learned how to walk forward."', '"Politics,Good,Walk"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"There are many ways of going forward, but only one way of standing still."', '"Wisdom,Way,Standing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"It is common sense to take a method and try it. If it fails, admit it frankly and try another. But above all, try something."', '"Common Sense,Try,Above"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"A nation that destroys its soils destroys itself. Forests are the lungs of our land, purifying the air and giving fresh strength to our people."', '"Strength,People,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Men are not prisoners of fate, but only prisoners of their own minds."', '"Men,Fate,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The only limit to our realization of tomorrow will be our doubts of today.', '"Today,Tomorrow,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"To reach a port, we must sail - sail, not tie at anchor - sail, not drift."', '"Anchor,Reach,Port"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Be sincere; be brief; be seated.', '"Sincere,Brief,Seated"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'True individual freedom cannot exist without economic security and independence. People who are hungry and out of a job are the stuff of which dictatorships are made.', '"Freedom,Independence,True"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"I\'m not the smartest fellow in the world, but I can sure pick smart colleagues."', '"Intelligence,Colleagues,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'I think we consider too much the good luck of the early bird and not enough the bad luck of the early worm.', '"Good,Chance,Bird"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Rules are not necessarily sacred, principles are."', '"Rules,Principles,Sacred"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"I pledge you, I pledge myself, to a new deal for the American people."', '"Myself,New,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Confidence... thrives on honesty, on honor, on the sacredness of obligations, on faithful protection and on unselfish performance. Without them it cannot live."', '"Confidence,Honesty,Honor"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"When you see a rattlesnake poised to strike, you do not wait until he has struck to crush him."', '"Wait,See,He"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Competition has been shown to be useful up to a certain point and no further, but cooperation, which is the thing we must strive for today, begins where competition leaves off."', '"Today,Competition,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Human kindness has never weakened the stamina or softened the fiber of a free people. A nation does not have to be cruel to be tough.', '"Kindness,Free,Tough"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'If you treat people right they will treat you right... ninety percent of the time.', '"Time,Treat,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'There is a mysterious cycle in human events. To some generations much is given. Of other generations much is expected. This generation of Americans has a rendezvous with destiny.', '"Destiny,Generation,Mysterious"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Nobody will ever deprive the American people of the right to vote except the American people themselves and the only way they could do this is by not voting.', '"Way,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The nation that destroys its soil destroys itself.', '"Nation,Soil,Itself"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"One thing is sure. We have to do something. We have to do the best we know how at the moment... If it doesn\'t turn out right, we can modify it as we go along."', '"Best,Moment,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'We are trying to construct a more inclusive society. We are going to make a country in which no one is left out.', '"Society,Country,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Self-interest is the enemy of all true affection.', '"True,Enemy,Affection"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The truth is found when men are free to pursue it.', '"Truth,Men,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Remember you are just an extra in everyone else\'s play.', '"Remember,Everyone,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Yesterday, December seventh, 1941, a date which will live in infamy, the United States of America was suddenly and deliberately attacked by naval and air forces of the Empire of Japan. We will gain the inevitable triumph, so help us God."', '"War,God,America"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Physical strength can never permanently withstand the impact of spiritual force.', '"Faith,Strength,Spiritual"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'It isn\'t sufficient just to want - you\'ve got to ask yourself what you are going to do to get the things you want.', '"Yourself,Things,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"More than an end to war, we want an end to the beginning of all wars - yes, an end to this brutal, inhuman and thoroughly impractical method of settling the differences between governments."', '"War,Beginning,Differences"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Prosperous farmers mean more employment, more prosperity for the workers and the business men of every industrial area in the whole country."', '"Business,Men,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The point in history at which we stand is full of promise and danger. The world will either move forward toward unity and widely shared prosperity - or it will move apart.', '"History,World,Unity"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'It is fun to be in the same decade with you.', '"Fun,Decade,Same"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"The only sure bulwark of continuing liberty is a government strong enough to protect the interests of the people, and a people strong enough and well enough informed to maintain its sovereign control over the goverment."', '"Freedom,Government,Control"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The school is the last expenditure upon which America should be willing to economize.', '"America,School,Last"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The virtues are lost in self-interest as rivers are lost in the sea.', '"Lost,Sea,Virtues"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'I do not look upon these United States as a finished product. We are still in the making.', '"Look,Product,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"In our personal ambitions we are individualists. But in our seeking for economic and political progress as a nation, we all go up or else all go down as one people."', '"Progress,Political,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"I am a Christian and a Democrat, that\'s all."', '"I Am,Christian,Democrat"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'If I went to work in a factory the first thing I\'d do is join a union.', '"Work,Join,First"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Not only our future economic soundness but the very soundness of our democratic institutions depends on the determination of our government to give employment to idle men.', '"Future,Men,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Here is my principle: Taxes shall be levied according to ability to pay. That is the only American principle.', '"American,Ability,Taxes"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'There is nothing I love as much as a good fight.', '"Love,Good,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Whoever seeks to set one religion against another seeks to destroy all religion.', '"Religion,Destroy,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'This generation of Americans has a rendezvous with destiny.', '"Destiny,Generation,Rendezvous"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'A reactionary is a somnambulist walking backwards.', '"Walking,Backwards,Reactionary"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Art is not a treasure in the past or an importation from another land, but part of the present life of all living and creating peoples."', '"Life,Art,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The United States Constitution has proved itself the most marvelously elastic compilation of rules of government ever written.', '"Government,Rules,Constitution"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'War is a contagion.', '"War,Contagion"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Don\'t forget what I discovered that over ninety percent of all national deficits from 1921 to 1939 were caused by payments for past, present, and future wars."', '"War,Future,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'It is an unfortunate human failing that a full pocketbook often groans more loudly than an empty stomach.', '"Stomach,Empty,More"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'It is the duty of the President to propose and it is the privilege of the Congress to dispose.', '"Duty,Privilege,Congress"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Those newspapers of the nation which most loudly cried dictatorship against me would have been the first to justify the beginnings of dictatorship by somebody else.', '"Me,Dictatorship,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'The overwhelming majority of Americans are possessed of two great qualities a sense of humor and a sense of proportion.', '"Humor,Great,Sense Of Humor"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'It takes a long time to bring the past up to the present.', '"Time,Long,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"In our seeking for economic and political progress, we all go up - or else we all go down."', '"Progress,Political,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'I am neither bitter nor cynical but I do wish there was less immaturity in political thinking.', '"Political,Thinking,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Favor comes because for a brief moment in the great space of human change and progress some general human purpose finds in him a satisfactory embodiment.', '"Change,Space,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Are you laboring under the impression that I read these memoranda of yours? I can\'t even lift them.', '"Lift,Yours,Impression"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'Our national determination to keep free of foreign wars and foreign entanglements cannot prevent us from feeling deep concern when ideals and principles that we have cherished are challenged.', '"Determination,Free,Principles"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"If we can boondoggle ourselves out of this depression, that word is going to be enshrined in the hearts of the American people for years to come."', '"People,American,Depression"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"But while they prate of economic laws, men and women are starving. We must lay hold of the fact that economic laws are not made by nature. They are made by human beings."', '"Nature,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'I believe that in every country the people themselves are more peaceably and liberally inclined than their governments.', '"Believe,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', '"Put two or three men in positions of conflicting authority. This will force them to work at loggerheads, allowing you to be the ultimate arbiter."', '"Work,Men,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'No group and no government can properly prescribe precisely what should constitute the body of knowledge with which true education is concerned.', '"Education,Knowledge,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'We continue to recognize the greater ability of some to earn more than others. But we do assert that the ambition of the individual to obtain for him a proper security is an ambition to be preferred to the appetite for great wealth and great power.', '"Power,Great,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'No government can help the destinies of people who insist in putting sectional and class consciousness ahead of general weal.', '"Government,People,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7c', 'We must lay hold of the fact that economic laws are not made by nature. They are made by human beings.', '"Nature,Human,Laws"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"We\'ve been merging with tools since the beginning of human evolution, and arguably, that\'s one of the things that makes us human beings."', '"Beginning,Evolution,Tools"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The biggest problem is that Facebook and Google are these giant feedback loops that give people what they want to hear. And when you use them in a world where your biases are being constantly confirmed, you become susceptible to fake news, propaganda, demagoguery."', '"World,News,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Trump has emphatically denied ties to Russia - a claim refuted by his Twitter feed and a cursory Google search. Putin says his government had nothing to do with the hack of the DNC computers, even though it carelessly left a trail of crumbs tracing back to his intelligence services. The cunning liar is exploiting the blundering one."', '"Intelligence,Government,Computers"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"In the epic war over Silicon Valley\'s intellectual property, Bill Gates was on the side of licensing copyright and robust protections for intellectual property. He wasn\'t on the side of the hackers, and he didn\'t want information to be free."', '"War,Hackers,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'My hope is that we revive \'monopoly\' as a core piece of political rhetoric that broadly denotes dominant firms with pernicious powers.', '"Hope,Political,Monopoly"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The sense of crisis is everything for Trump - even if it\'s largely invented. His depiction of darkness justifies his candidacy, the need to violently shake the system. His ability to conjure fear is what distinguished him from all those career pols he has vanquished. And it suits his ego."', '"Fear,Darkness,Ego"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Google is arguably one of the greatest inventions. The search engine is one of the greatest inventions in human history.', '"History,Search,Search Engine"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Along with Facebook, Microsoft, and Apple, these companies are in a race to become our \'personal assistant.\' They want to wake us in the morning, have their artificial intelligence software guide us through our days, and never quite leave our sides."', '"Morning,Intelligence,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"What I worry about ultimately is that when we\'re stripped of our privacy, when we\'re stripped of free will, when we start to merge with machines in a more robust way, at some point, we\'ll cease to be identifiably human. And therefore, I think our humanity is, in some ways, the thing that\'s under existential threat."', '"Humanity,Free,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Mark Zuckerberg talks about telepathy, and Elon Musk has invested in trying to create a brain-machine interface."', '"Create,Trying,About"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'An article in the \'Moscow Times\' described Trump as the city\'s first grand builder since Stalin.', '"City,First,Builder"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The genesis of Donald Trump\'s relationship with Paul Manafort begins with Roy Cohn. That Roy Cohn: Joe McCarthy\'s heavy-lidded henchman, lawyer to the Genovese family. During the \'70s, Trump and his father hired Cohn as their lawyer to defend the family against a housing discrimination suit."', '"Family,Relationship,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"On its face, Donald Trump\'s hateful musings about women and his boastful claims of sexual dominance should be reason alone to drive him from polite society and certainly to blockade him from the West Wing. Yet somehow, his misogyny has instead propelled his campaign to the brink of the Republican nomination."', '"Alone,Women,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Google helps us sort the Internet by providing a sense of hierarchy to information. Facebook uses its algorithms and its intricate understanding of our social circles to filter the news we encounter. Amazon bestrides book publishing with its overwhelming hold on that market.', '"Internet,Information,News"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"My dad has been in the fight against monopoly since it wasn\'t so cool. I\'m sure I\'ve turned to the subject to please him, though I think he might consider some of my arguments a little flamethrowing for his tastes."', '"Cool,Dad,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Brazil is a country largely resistant to ideology. This is a strange fact given its founding by followers of the French philosopher Auguste Comte, who inscribed an epigram from his philosophy of positivism in the national flag: Order and Progress."', '"Progress,Country,Flag"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"If you think of data as kind of an x-ray of our soul, it\'s this window into our minds that the company has possessed. It\'s a very, very powerful x-ray for them to hold because the more that you understand about somebody, the easier it is to manipulate them."', '"Window,Soul,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Putin has made a habit of supporting far-right candidates who undermine his foes in Europe; perhaps he never could have imagined such a character taking root on American soil. Trump\'s reasons for aligning with Putin have been more innocent, if no less dangerous."', '"Character,Habit,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'I have really no desire to go back into management ever again.', '"Management,Back,Desire"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Monopolists always defend their monopolies by arguing that competition is wasteful. When the railroad barons completed their monopoly, they argued it would be wasteful to have competing rail lines, AT&T said the same thing. But today, the size and scope of these monopolies is different."', '"Today,Competition,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"When I started off in journalism, you knew there was an audience out there and that you wanted people to read what you produced. But it also felt like you had a limited ability to shape the audience, or to acquire an audience, for what you were doing. So you didn\'t really think too much about that."', '"Journalism,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"If you game Facebook and Google in the right way, then you can achieve a mass audience."', '"Game,Way,Achieve"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Of course, formulas always existed in journalism. When I was just getting into the business, \'Time\' and \'Newsweek\' knew if they could put Jesus\' face on the cover that it would do really well on the newsstands. So every year, they would put Jesus\' face on the newsstand. There was a formula there."', '"Business,Time,Face"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Once upon a time, if you were going to get a loan from me, I would have had to look at your file, and I would have to make a decision about whether youre going to get a loan. Maybe we would meet and talk about it. There would be some level of human involvement and human interaction. Now, a lot of this is determined by an algorithm."', '"Time,Look,Decision"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"I grew up using maps and having a sense of direction, and now I have a phone. I used to try to remember numbers, and now I... can just call them up instantly. And that\'s great. But what\'s happening right now is that we\'re in a phase of human evolution where we\'re merging with machines."', '"Great,Remember,Direction"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The Internet was invented in an age when our entire approach to regulation has been extremely lax, and so you\'d think, \'OK, there might be a law on the books that governs how these corporations can handle our data.\'"', '"Age,Internet,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"There\'s this proud American tradition of worrying about the power of communication companies. That going all the way back to the founding, we\'ve tried to limit the power of monopolies that played a role in our democracy."', '"Communication,Power,Democracy"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Google\'s ability to pick winners and losers in the information world is a menace. These companies have the ability to determine which media companies are successful and which ones are failures. If I adopt a business plan that doesn\'t line up with Google\'s, then they\'re not going to reward me."', '"Business,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"If I\'m reading my Facebook feed, it\'s using algorithms, procedures, and methods to give me what I want, or what it thinks that I want, or what suits its business plan."', '"Business,Me,Plan"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Booksellers initially thought of Amazon as their best friend. They were coming in, and they were challenging Barnes and Noble, and Borders, which were the big, dominant corporations of the day, and that they would disrupt them and make them less powerful, but they could never envision that Amazon would overtake them all."', '"Best,Day,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Apple was very important in terms of disrupting the music business and remaking the television business. They made it harder for people to make money on the things that they produce. In news, they\'ve created Apple News, and they\'ve tried to steer people towards information."', '"Business,Money,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"From the start, the promise of Jurgen Klinsmann as manager of the U.S. men\'s national team was revolution: gritty, plodding American soccer would give way to attacking flair; the parade of journeymen would end; an era of skilled stylists would begin."', '"Men,Way,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Michael Bradley has the stuff of leadership; he works hard and can break up the opponent\'s play. However, that\'s not enough to justify his philanthropic attitude towards possession, the generous portion of balls that he contributes to his foes. His sloppiness constantly culminates in unnecessary goals."', '"Attitude,Leadership,Goals"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'There\'s no reason why there needs to be one search engine or one social network or one store that we buy all of our crap from. It\'s possible to imagine a world in which there\'s actually competition.', '"World,Competition,Search"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Who can complain about the price that Google is charging you? Or who can complain about Amazon\'s prices; they are simply lower than the competition\'s. And that\'s why I think we need to shift back to a more Brandeisian conception of antitrust, where we consider values other than simply efficiency and low prices."', '"Competition,Efficiency,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"I\'m reading the way a lot of technology executives have decried \'gatekeepers\' and \'traditional media,\' and that one of the promises of \'new media\' was that it would break the chokehold that old media companies had on public opinion."', '"Technology,Media,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Once upon a time, gatekeepers were newspaper publishers and magazine editors and people who ran radio stations and news networks. And they decided what went above the fold and what went on page A10."', '"Time,News,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Trump and Yanukovych have shared the same political brain: an operative named Paul Manafort.', '"Brain,Political,Same"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Ukrainians use the term \'political technologist\' as a favored synonym for electoral consultant. Trump turned to Manafort for what seemed at first a technical task: Manafort knows how to bullwhip and wheedle delegates at a contested convention.', '"Political,Task,First"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"As the 2016 campaign has graphically illustrated, Trump doesn\'t treat rivals gently. Testifying before a congressional committee in 1993, he began with his rote protestations of friendship."', '"Friendship,Treat,Committee"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"There are, in fact, apps you can use to measure how many times you check your phone, and I shudder to think how many times I check my phone. I\'m sure it would be probably in the hundreds of times that I check over the course of the day."', '"Day,Phone,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Mark Zuckerberg has never really had pressure put on him. He\'s an engineer, and he\'s created this perfect system that is Facebook, and he\'s always been concerned about the internal beauty and logic of this creation that he\'s created. I don\'t think that the human implications of what he\'s created have often been apparent to him."', '"Beauty,Perfect,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"I look at the way that my kids interact with technology, and it becomes a mirror to the ways in which I myself interact with technology. I can see the ways in which that addiction and compulsion starts to settle in on them, and it\'s much more unnerving to see it in them than it is to experience it myself."', '"Experience,Technology,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Not even Trump\'s father\'s wealth, nor his father\'s faith in his son\'s destiny, could save Trump from incessant discipline. At the age of 13, he was shipped off to the New York Military Academy, which employed brutal tactics for the remaking of delinquent character, even resorting to violence to assert control over the boys."', '"Faith,Age,Discipline"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Trump considers himself such a virile example of masculinity that he\'s qualified to serve as the ultimate arbiter of femininity. He relishes judging women on the basis of their looks, which he seems to believe amounts to the sum of their character."', '"Women,Character,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Our faith in technology is no longer fully consistent with our belief in liberty.', '"Faith,Technology,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"As parents, we have kids who reflect back to us our addiction to devices, and we have all sorts of worries about whether this is a healthy thing."', '"Parents,Back,Addiction"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'It\'s very un-American to say nice things about elites. Elites are often terrible. It\'s not like we\'ve ever had a perfect set of benevolent democratic elites ruling over our country. But the fact of the matter is that a representative system of democracy delegates power to elites.', '"Power,Democracy,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"When you\'re staring at your phone to navigate and being led places, you do become less aware of your environment, and the journey becomes kind of automated. There is an aliveness that comes with having to puzzle out directions for yourself. And you have to ask other people for help, which creates opportunity for social connection."', '"Journey,Opportunity,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'The greatest miracle of the Internet is that it exists - the second greatest is that it persists.', '"Internet,Miracle,Greatest"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Hunting for malware requires highly specialized knowledge of the intricacies of the domain name system - the protocol that allows us to type email addresses and website names to initiate communication. DNS enables our words to set in motion a chain of connections between servers, which in turn delivers the results we desire."', '"Knowledge,Communication,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Computer scientists have built a set of massive DNS databases, which provide fragmentary histories of communications flows, in part to create an archive of malware: a kind of catalog of the tricks bad actors have tried to pull, which often involve masquerading as legitimate actors."', '"Bad,Create,Tried"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"I\'d actually argue that the best thing to happen to the \'Washington Post\' was hiring Marty Baron, maybe the greatest newspaper editor of his generation."', '"Best,Generation,Newspaper"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The first book advance I got was paid out in thirds. And over time, as I\'ve had different deals, the advances get chopped up into ever-smaller parcels."', '"Time,First,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Self-publishing is fine. But in a world of self-publishing, where everything is about what you get on the back end, there\'s a serious disincentive from embarking on really important, vital projects."', '"World,Important,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"I think what\'s happening with book advances is something that most of the world just doesn\'t fully appreciate, especially when it comes to nonfiction, because writing a book of investigative journalism is an expensive endeavor, and the system works best if you have publishers making bets on authors."', '"Best,Journalism,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Donald Trump\'s interest in Russia dates back to Soviet times. In fact, there\'s extraordinary footage of him shaking hands with Mikhail Gorbachev. It comes from 1988, the peak of perestroika and Gorbachev\'s efforts to charm the American public."', '"Hands,Back,American"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"One of Trump\'s vulnerabilities is that he doesn\'t always vet his people, whether it\'s business partners, the dubious characters he retweets, or the foreign leaders who show up at his door."', '"Business,Door,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Having a friend in the Kremlin would help Trump fulfill his longtime dream of planting his name in the Moscow skyline - a dream that he pursued even as he organized his presidential campaign.', '"Name,Help,Campaign"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"There\'s an oft-used shorthand for the technologist\'s view of the world. It is assumed that libertarianism dominates Silicon Valley, and that isn\'t wholly wrong. High-profile devotees of Ayn Rand can be found there."', '"View,World,Valley"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Privacy won\'t survive the present trajectory of technology - and with the sense of being perpetually watched, humans will behave more cautiously, less subversively. Our ideas about the competitive marketplace are at risk."', '"Technology,Privacy,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"When the mayor of Sao Paulo wanted to increase bus fare by 21 centavos in 2013, the country erupted in the largest mass protests in its history. It wasn\'t a dramatic hike - just nine cents - but a perfect symbol of the increasing burdens on the working poor, forced to fend with an inadequate system, insensitive to their plight."', '"History,Perfect,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Brazil is strewn with ruins of projects - refineries, power plants - begun but never finished. Most of this investment never landed in places or industries that really meshed with the trajectory of the global economy. This wasn\'t state-of-the art industrial policy. The projects seemed curiously nostalgic."', '"Art,Power,Investment"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Trump uses the phrase \'America First,\' only dimly aware that he is repeating a phrase from the interwar years and indifferent to its historic resonances. But he compulsively echoes that period - another time when leaders described the world in apocalyptic terms."', '"Time,World,America"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', 'Trump is a real estate guy who sucks up to power to get buildings built.', '"Power,Real,Buildings"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"We think of Netflix as a great personalization machine. It understands how you love French midcentury cinema and British murder mysteries, so examples of those pop up in your personalization engine. But you\'re also getting fed a lot of Netflix content."', '"Love,Great,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"If you\'re presented with choices that steer you toward your worst instincts, that\'s what you\'ll choose. If I\'m presented with Snickers bars, I won\'t necessarily seek out kale."', '"Choices,Worst,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"When Trump started belittling him, Jeb reverted to Bush form. He couldn\'t understand how anyone could question his noble pursuit of public service. In the face of Trump\'s attacks, he looked hurt and stunned."', '"Face,Service,Public Service"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"The demise of Jeb Bush has been a source of immeasurable pleasure for, well, nearly everyone."', '"Pleasure,Everyone,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"In 2012, Vladimir Putin returned to the presidency after a four-year, constitutionally imposed hiatus. It wasn\'t the smoothest of transitions. To his surprise, in the run-up to his inauguration, protesters filled the streets of Moscow and other major cities to denounce his comeback."', '"Comeback,Surprise,Hiatus"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"After the global financial crisis of 2008, populist uprisings had sprouted across Europe. Putin and his strategists sensed the beginnings of a larger uprising that could upend the Continent and make life uncomfortable for his geostrategic competitors."', '"Life,Uncomfortable,Crisis"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"Gay marriage is a divisive issue in France, where Fillon has vowed to block adoption by same-sex couples. The battle against Islamism also remains a rallying cry; Fillon\'s campaign manifesto is called \'Conquering Islamic Totalitarianism\'."', '"Marriage,Battle,Gay"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7d', '"In mid-2014, 51 percent of American Republicans viewed Putin very unfavorably. Two years later, 14 percent did. By January, 75 percent of Republicans said Trump had the \'right approach\' toward Russia."', '"American,Right,Russia"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Every life is precious to God. God created every one of us. He gave us a soul, and that soul will live as long as God lives."', '"Life,God,Soul"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'All I know is that I\'m a sinner and that God has forgiven me of my sins. Because I put my faith and trust in Jesus Christ.', '"Faith,God,Trust"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'We have taken God out of our education system. We have taken Him out of government. You have lawyers that sue you every time you mention the name of Jesus Christ in any public forum.', '"Education,God,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I believe Donald Trump is a good man. He did everything wrong as a candidate, and he won, and I don\'t understand it. Other than I think God put him there."', '"God,Good,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"We are losing our country and the freedoms we have enjoyed. As Bible-believing Christians, we are the ones who must take action before it\'s too late."', '"Action,Country,Late"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I\'m at least smart enough to know I could never fill Billy Graham\'s shoes, but I\'m grateful he gave me an opportunity to help him finish his race on earth well and to continue his life\'s work."', '"Life,Work,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I\'ve never really been one to try to be politically correct. I just feel truth is truth, and sometimes I probably offend some people."', '"Truth,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I have never really tried to forge my own identity. As followers of Jesus Christ, we ought to forge our identity in Him."', '"Jesus Christ,Identity,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'I was 22 years old when I asked Christ to come into my heart. You cannot be born a Christian; you can only be converted. And that is by putting your faith and trust in Christ.', '"Faith,Trust,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'The world is attacking Christians because they hate the name of Christ. And President Trump has been defending Christians.', '"Hate,World,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"During my teens and early 20s, I proved to be anything but what most people expected Billy Graham\'s son to be. I\'m so thankful he never gave up on me or quit loving me."', '"Thankful,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I just believe as a Christian, we are to show love; we are to show compassion to people, not to point the finger, not to do this, but to do this - to love them, to welcome them, to embrace them."', '"Love,Believe,Welcome"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"When my mother passed away, we knew what she wanted on her tombstone, so I asked my father, so there wouldn\'t be any argument among us children, \'Daddy, what do you want on your tombstone?\' He thought about that. He said, \'preacher.\' So that\'s what\'s going to be on his tombstone. Preacher."', '"Father,Children,Argument"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"It\'s hard to pin down what it means to be an evangelical today. It\'s been diluted quite a bit. It is a powerful voting bloc, no question, but they\'re liberal as well as conservative - and they\'re made of Latinos, blacks, whites."', '"Today,Conservative,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I think Newt Gingrich is a Christian; at least, he told me he is."', '"Me,Think,He"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'The Muslims want to force conversion. Christians want to persuade you to voluntarily change your heart to where you would say yes to Jesus Christ.', '"Change,Heart,Jesus Christ"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I saw my father preach in Madison Square Garden, and I was a little embarrassed, I think, the first time I heard him preach. That\'s my father up there, and I kind of slid down in my chair."', '"Time,Father,Chair"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'Only God can turn our nation and the hearts of its people.', '"God,People,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"God empowered him; and my father, when he stood to preach, he wasn\'t preaching his message, he was preaching God\'s message."', '"God,Father,Preaching"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Syria, for all its problems, at least has a constitution that guarantees equal protection of citizens. Around the world, we have seen that this is essential where Christians are a minority and are not protected."', '"World,Problems,Constitution"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"In my opinion, Putin is right on these issues. Obviously, he may be wrong about many things, but he has taken a stand to protect his nation\'s children from the damaging effects of any gay and lesbian agenda."', '"Gay,Children,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Jesus Christ came for me, and he came for each person that is infected with HIV/AIDS. God loves that person. He doesn\'t hate them. They\'ve made mistakes. We\'ve all made mistakes. But God loves them, God cares for them, and Jesus Christ died for their sins."', '"God,Hate,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Jesus wasn\'t real loving sometimes. He called the Pharisees vipers, snakes, whitewashed tombs. So, you have to understand the world in which we live is dangerous."', '"World,Sometimes,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'A secular worldview hostile to biblical values has overrun our culture and permeated our government.', '"Government,Culture,Values"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I regret any comments I have ever made which may have cast any doubt on the personal faith of our president, Mr. Obama."', '"Faith,Regret,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Rather than seeking to stem the tide, our educators, politicians, and judges aid the advance of godlessness. This cannot continue if our children and grandchildren are to live in a country that still recognises God and upholds religious liberty."', '"God,Children,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"We certainly love the Muslim people. But that is not the faith of this country. And that is not the religion that built this nation. The people of the Christian faith and the Jewish faith are the ones who built America, and it is not Islam."', '"Love,Faith,Religion"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'There is no question that America has been a nation that has been blessed by almighty God. There is no other nation in the history of mankind that has done what His nation has done - and it\'s because of God\'s hand and His blessing.', '"God,History,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'I don\'t think I\'ve been to any country where everybody was supportive - there\'s always churches or groups who don\'t like my theology or that we associate with this group or that group.', '"Country,Always,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"God\'s word is the same, yesterday and today and a million years from now."', '"God,Today,Yesterday"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'Most Christians would not recognize Mormonism as part of the Christian faith.', '"Faith,Would,Christian"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"You have to look at what a person does with his life. Anyone can say that he\'s a Christian, but you look at how they live."', '"Life,Look,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'I think AIDS can be won. I think we can win this fight. It is winnable. But it means behavior change.', '"Change,Fight,Behavior"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Everybody\'s got their phone up and everybody\'s taking recordings and posting it on YouTube and whatever and sending it to you, and it gets shown around the world."', '"World,YouTube,Phone"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'We\'re in a sick world.', '"World,Sick"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'Gay couples cannot have children. All they can do is recruit your child.', '"Gay,Children,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"Our country\'s got a sin problem, and I believe if these politicians in Washington would recognize the moral failure of so many of their policies that maybe we could fix it."', '"Failure,Believe,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'We are all flawed people.', '"People,Flawed"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'I don\'t condone bad language.', '"Bad,Language,Condone"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'I don\'t have any faith in the Republican Party. I don\'t have any faith in the Democrat Party. The only hope for this nation is God.', '"Faith,God,Hope"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"The God of Islam is not the same God of the Judaeo-Christian faith. The God that we worship in Christianity is a God that has a Son. To Islam, that is blasphemy, to say that God has a son. Therefore, they do not worship the God that we worship."', '"Faith,God,Son"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"My father has been faithful to the calling that God gave him: that is, to preach the Gospel... He has presented Christ to every person that God has put before him."', '"God,Father,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', '"I want to take my life and the time I have on this earth to try to tell others about Jesus, that Jesus Christ is God\'s son who took our sins to the Cross and shed His blood for our sins."', '"Life,God,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'Billy Graham that the world saw on television or saw on the big screen was the same Billy Graham that we saw at home. He wasn\'t two people.', '"Home,World,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7e', 'The man the world knew as Billy Graham was always \'Daddy\' to me. I was well into my teens before I fully comprehended that my father had a household name and a worldwide ministry.', '"Man,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', 'For you are the makers of the flag and it is well that you glory in the making.', '"Patriotism,Glory,Flag"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', 'My stars and my stripes are your dream and your labors.', '"Patriotism,Stars,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', '"A public office is not a job, it is an opportunity to do something for the public."', '"Opportunity,Job,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', 'I have hardly seen my baby for six weeks; have been at the office from nine A.M. to eleven P.M. regularly.', '"Baby,Seen,Six"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', '"Newspaper men, perhaps more than any other class, are rated by ability."', '"Men,Newspaper,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', 'No man should have a political office because he wants a job.', '"Political,Man,Job"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', '"It is work and personal worth which make a State great both politically and industrially, and in my estimation they are to be found in largest proportions in the Democratic party."', '"Work,Great,Worth"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe7f', 'I am not the flag: not at all. I am but its shadow.', '"Shadow,I Am,Flag"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Love doesn\'t make the world go \'round. Love is what makes the ride worthwhile.', '"Love,Love Is,Ride"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Bravery is being the only one who knows you\'re afraid.', '"Courage,Afraid,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Scratch a dog and you\'ll find a permanent job.', '"Pet,Permanent,Dog"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Experience enables you to recognize a mistake when you make it again.', '"Experience,Mistake,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', '"You can learn many things from children. How much patience you have, for instance."', '"Patience,Parenting,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', '"When you get something for nothing, you just haven\'t been billed for it yet."', '"Nothing,Something,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'It\'s a strange world of language in which skating on thin ice can get you into hot water.', '"Water,World,Hot"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Originality is the art of concealing your source.', '"Art,Your,Source"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'One advantage of talking to yourself is that you know at least somebody\'s listening.', '"Funny,Yourself,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', '"Honest criticism is hard to take, particularly from a relative, a friend, an acquaintance or a stranger."', '"Criticism,Stranger,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'The trouble with being punctual is that nobody\'s there to appreciate it.', '"Nobody,Trouble,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'You never realize what a good memory you have until you try to forget something.', '"Good,Memory,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Experience is that marvelous thing that enables you to recognize a mistake when you make it again.', '"Experience,Mistake,Marvelous"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Anybody who thinks talk is cheap should get some legal advice.', '"Legal,Advice,Talk"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'The most efficient labor-saving device is still money.', '"Money,Still,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Nothing makes you more tolerant of a neighbor\'s noisy party than being there.', '"Nothing,Neighbor,More"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', '"Nothing makes it easier to resist temptation than a proper bringing-up, a sound set of values - and witnesses."', '"Nothing,Temptation,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'What makes resisting temptation difficult for many people is they don\'t want to discourage it completely.', '"Difficult,People,Temptation"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'An autobiography usually reveals nothing bad about its writer except his memory.', '"Memory,Bad,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Children are unpredictable. You never know what inconsistency they\'re going to catch you in next.', '"Children,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'It\'s the opinion of some that crops could be grown on the moon; which raises the fear that it may not be long before we\'re paying somebody not to.', '"Fear,Moon,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'The easiest way to solve a problem is to pick an easy one.', '"Way,Easy,Problem"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'You\'re an old-timer if you can remember when setting the world on fire was a figure of speech.', '"Fire,World,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
