	('399795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'Anybody who finds it easy to make money on the horses is probably in the dog food business.', '"Business,Money,Food"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe80', 'One trouble with developing speed reading skills is that by the time you realize a book is boring you\'ve already finished it.', '"Time,Boring,Speed"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe81', '"Frequently the more trifling the subject, the more animated and protracted the discussion."', '"More,Discussion,Subject"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe81', 'With the Union my best and dearest earthly hopes are entwined.', '"Best,Hopes,Union"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe81', 'The dangers of a concentration of all power in the general government of a confederacy so vast as ours are too obvious to be disregarded.', '"Power,Government,Concentration"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe81', 'A Republic without parties is a complete anomaly. The histories of all popular governments show absurd is the idea of their attempting to exist without parties.', '"Absurd,Without,Exist"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Nothing is more responsible for the good old days than a bad memory.', '"Good,Good Old Days,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Health is the thing that makes you feel that now is the best time of the year.', '"Best,Health,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'I find that a great part of the information I have was acquired by looking up something and finding something else on the way.', '"Great,Information,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Christmas is over and Business is Business.', '"Business,Christmas,Over"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'What this country needs is a good five-cent nickel.', '"Good,Country,Needs"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Elections are won by men and women chiefly because most people vote against somebody rather than for somebody.', '"Women,Men,People"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Too much truth is uncouth.', '"Truth,Too Much,Truth Is"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', '"The true republic: men, their rights and nothing more; women, their rights and nothing less."', '"Women,Men,True"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Having imagination it takes you an hour to write a paragraph that if you were unimaginative would take you only a minute.', '"Imagination,Paragraph,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'Middle age occurs when you are too young to take up golf and too old to rush up to the net.', '"Age,Young,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', '"The trouble with this country is that there are too many politicians who believe, with a conviction based on experience, that you can fool all of the people all of the time."', '"Experience,Time,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'There must be a day or two in a man\'s life when he is the precise age for something important.', '"Life,Age,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'There are plenty of good five cent cigars in the country. The trouble is they cost a quarter.', '"Good,Country,Trouble"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'We have nothing in our history or position to invite aggression; we have everything to beckon us to the cultivation of relations of peace and amity with all nations.', '"History,Peace,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', '"Years ago we discovered the exact point, the dead center of middle age. It occurs when you are too young to take up golf and too old to rush up to the net."', '"Age,Dead,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe82', 'You do not know what you can miss before you try.', '"Know,Try,Miss"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"The automatic stabilizer is unemployment insurance, food stamps, additional coverage of Medicaid."', '"Food,Insurance,Unemployment"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"That is - the reason for that is that home prices are only going to go up. Now, they\'ve never gone down nationwide in our - since we\'ve been keeping track of this."', '"Home,Never,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"We are shrinking the size of the federal government as a percent of our economy from over 21 percent of the economy to 19 percent of the economy. At the same time, we\'re growing the private economy."', '"Time,Government,Size"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Right now we think that rates will stay low, that you\'ll be able to get a mortgage below seven percent and that\'s kicked off a refinance boom that\'s going to put more money in the pockets of consumers."', '"Money,Will,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, you know, we\'ve got a lot of stimulus in the economy already from the tax cut, from the lowered interest rates, and also from the refinancing of mortgages."', '"Know,Well,Interest"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', 'And so we have to be careful with looking at additional stimulus that we don\'t provoke an increase in the bond rate and then offset a lot of the stimulus we\'ve already got.', '"Bond,Looking,Careful"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"I think if you go beyond a year - if this continues into the system in the out years, I think there is a risk and that - that we could have a negative reaction in the bond market and that will offset the good that was attempted to be done."', '"Good,Bond,Negative"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', 'And so the danger for the housing industry is if we see interest rates rise.', '"Rise,See,Housing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"So from the housing standpoint, steady as you go, I think, would be the best medicine."', '"Best,Medicine,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, I think the best form would be to put money directly in the pockets of consumers."', '"Best,Money,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, we\'re just now seeing the reductions in mortgage rates. The mortgage rates are based on the ten-year rate and the Fed controls the overnight or the shorter rates."', '"Seeing,Well,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', 'We think if the economy remains weak that we could see mortgage rates trail down and we think that we could see rates below seven percent into early next year.', '"See,Down,Next"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"They flooded liquidity in the marketplace but the mortgage rate is based much more on expectations of inflation. So if the average investor believes that there is inflation coming, they\'ll move that rate up."', '"Expectations,Inflation,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', 'Right now the long-term investors are telling us that they\'re not as concerned about inflation and so we\'re seeing these rates now move into the marketplace and out to the street - rates that individuals can get.', '"Street,Inflation,Seeing"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, I think as long as people are talking about stimulus, I think the Fed will be thinking about cutting rates because monetary policy is the better way to go because you can turn it on and turn it off."', '"Thinking,Long,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"And so Fannie Mae produces very strong results for investors in - when interest rates are high and when interest rates are low, in recession and during booms."', '"Strong,High,Interest"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, now, and there\'s - for every dollar the federal government spends, there\'s real people on the other side, and so when we talk about reductions that are going to affect providers, that\'s going to affect hospitals and doctors and others."', '"Government,People,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"Well, there are about 10 million children that aren\'t covered by health insurance. About 3 million qualify for Medicaid but don\'t get it, so we\'re going to reach out and bring more of those kids into the Medicaid program."', '"Health,Children,Insurance"', '2023-05-29 12:04:00', '2023-05-29 12:04:00'),
	('399835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe83', '"If there\'s a severe recession, the automatic stabilizers will come into effect, and we will still try to reduce the structural deficit, but we will not try to keep cutting the budget so that we keep worsening a severe recession."', '"Will,Try,Budget"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I am personally not against keeping animals at zoos, as they serve a huge educational purpose, but treating them well and with respect seems the least we could do, and with \'we\' I mean not just zoo staff, but most certainly also the public."', '"Respect,Purpose,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Human morality is unthinkable without empathy.', '"Empathy,Morality,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Our brains have been designed to blur the line between self and other. It is an ancient neural circuitry that marks every mammal, from mouse to elephant."', '"Elephant,Blur,Self"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The enemy of science is not religion. Religion comes in endless shapes and forms... The true enemy is the substitution of thought, reflection, and curiosity with dogma."', '"Science,Religion,Reflection"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Empathy probably started out as a mechanism to improve maternal care. Mammalian mothers who were attentive to their young\'s needs were more likely to rear successful offspring.', '"Empathy,Care,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"People want to work with somebody who feels shame, who worries about the perceptions of others. Dishonesty is something we don\'t like in others."', '"Work,People,Shame"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Unlike the primate hand, the elephant\'s grasping organ is also its nose. Elephants use their trunks not only to reach food but also to sniff and touch it. With their unparalleled sense of smell, the animals know exactly what they are going for. Vision is secondary."', '"Food,Vision,Elephant"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'I describe in \'Chimpanzee Politics\' how the alpha male needs broad support to reach the top spot. He needs some close allies and he needs many group members to be on his side.', '"Politics,Support,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Popular culture bombards us with examples of animals being humanized for all sorts of purposes, ranging from education to entertainment to satire to propaganda. Walt Disney, for example, made us forget that Mickey is a mouse, and Donald a duck. George Orwell laid a cover of human societal ills over a population of livestock."', '"Education,Culture,Duck"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'The sturdiest pillars of human morality are compassion and a sense of justice.', '"Justice,Compassion,Morality"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Religion looms as large as an elephant in the United States, to the point that being nonreligious is about the biggest handicap a politician running for office can have, bigger than being gay, unmarried, thrice married, or black."', '"Religion,Black,Gay"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Chimps cannot tell us anything about peaceful relations, because chimps have only different degrees of hostility between communities. Whereas bonobos do tell us something; they tell us about the possibility of having peaceful relationships."', '"Anything,Tell,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I think the sense of fairness in humans is very strongly developed, and that\'s why we react so strongly to all the bonuses received by Wall Street executives. We want to know why they deserve these benefits."', '"Street,React,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'War is evitable if conditions are such that the costs of making war are higher than the benefits.', '"War,Higher,Costs"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Octopuses have hundreds of suckers, each one equipped with its own ganglion with thousands of neurons. These \'mini-brains\' are interconnected, making for a widely distributed nervous system. That is why a severed octopus arm may crawl on its own and even pick up food."', '"Food,Own,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Female bonobos form a strong sisterhood. They rule through female solidarity.', '"Solidarity,Through,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"It is well known that apes in the wild offer spontaneous assistance to each other, defending against leopards, say, or consoling distressed companions with tender embraces."', '"Wild,Spontaneous,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Darwin wasn\'t just provocative in saying that we descend from the apes - he didn\'t go far enough. We are apes in every way, from our long arms and tailless bodies to our habits and temperament."', '"Long,Way,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"It is hard to get animals which normally pay little attention to each other to do things together. One can teach dolphins to jump simultaneously out of the water precisely because they show similar behavior spontaneously, but try to make two domestic cats jump together and you will fail."', '"Water,Together,Behavior"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"There has been so much underestimating of animal cognition that to perhaps overestimate it, as I probably do, is probably a healthy reaction."', '"Animal,Reaction,Healthy"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Following rules is, of course, the reason the dog is man\'s best friend is because the dog follows rules, and they actually do experiments on that, is that how well certain breeds of dogs follow rules, and how much they internalize them. And so many hierarchical animals, obviously they follow rules."', '"Best,Man,Rules"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I was raised Catholic. Not just a little bit Catholic, like my wife, Catherine. When she was young, many Catholics in France already barely went to church, except for the big three: baptism, marriage, and funeral. And only the middle one was by choice."', '"Marriage,Wife,Choice"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The whole reason people fill their homes with furry carnivores and not with, say, iguanas and turtles, is because mammals offer something no reptile ever will. They give affection, they want affection, and respond to our emotions the way we do to theirs."', '"Emotions,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Bonobo studies started in the \'70s and came to fruition in the \'80s. Then in the \'90s, all of a sudden, boom, they ended because of the warfare in the Congo. It was really bad for the bonobo and ironic that people with their warfare were preventing us from studying the hippies of the primate world."', '"World,Bad,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Religion may have become a codification of morality, and it may fortify it, but it\'s not the origin of it."', '"Religion,Morality,Origin"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"What is the evolutionary value of blushing? It seems not to be to our advantage to do it, to involuntarily reveal our inner emotions. If we\'re trying to manipulate or lie, actions in furtherance of individual goals as opposed to the goals of others, blushing would not seem to be helpful. And yet everyone blushes, except the psychopath."', '"Goals,Value,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Chimpanzees have very strong preferences and aversions that are completely personality-linked. The people who are unsuccessful in working with chimpanzees are those who take this personally.', '"People,Strong,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"There\'s a long tradition in Western thought that humans are not shackled by biology, whereas animals are pure instinct machines."', '"Long,Biology,Pure"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"When humans behave murderously, such as inflicting senseless slaughter of innocents in warfare, we like to blame it on some dark, \'animalistic\' instinct."', '"Blame,Dark,Behave"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Many economists are great believers in the idea that everything in nature is competitive and that we should set up a society which is competitive to reflect that. Anyone who cannot keep up, well, too bad."', '"Nature,Great,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I have often noticed how primate groups in their entirety enter a similar mood. All of a sudden, all of them are playful, hopping around. Or all of them are grumpy. Or all of them are sleepy and settle down. In such cases, the mood contagion serves the function of synchronizing activities."', '"Mood,Down,Playful"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"If you look at human society, it is very easy, of course, to compare our warfare and territoriality with the chimpanzee. But that\'s only one side of what we do. We also trade, we intermarry, we allow each other to travel through our territory. There\'s an enormous amount of cooperation."', '"Society,Travel,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Closeness to animals creates the desire to understand them, and not just a little piece of them, but the whole animal. It makes us wonder what goes on in their heads even though we fully realize that the answer can only be approximated."', '"Animal,Desire,Realize"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Deep down, creationists realize they will never win factual arguments with science. This is why they have construed their own science-like universe, known as Intelligent Design, and eagerly jump on every tidbit of information that seems to go their way."', '"Science,Design,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'A chimpanzee who is really gearing up for a fight doesn\'t waste time with gestures but just goes ahead and attacks.', '"Time,Fight,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The fact that the apes exist and that we can study them is extremely important and makes us reflect on ourselves and our human nature. In that sense alone, you need to protect the apes."', '"Alone,Nature,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Very long ago our ancestors had moral systems. Our current institutions are only a couple of thousand years old, which is really not old in the eyes of a biologist."', '"Eyes,Long,Ancestors"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I\'m personally a nonbeliever, so I\'m struggling with if we really need religion."', '"Religion,Need,Personally"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Personally, I think it is possible to build a society that is moral on a nonreligious basis, but the jury is still out on that."', '"Society,Possible,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'You should know as much as you can about the human species if you have a hand in designing human society.', '"Society,Know,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"After World War II it was decided that, in order to prevent the Germans and the French from having another war, it would be better to tie them together into one economic pact so they would invest in each other and have mutual stakes. Until now, that has worked to prevent warfare between the two."', '"War,Together,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"If you look at national economies today, for example, the American economy, the European economy, the Indians, the Chinese, we\'re all tied together. If one of them sinks, the rest are going to sink with them and if one floats, the rest are lifted up. I find that very interesting."', '"Today,Together,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"If there is any form of contagion that is adaptive, it is the immediate response to the fear of others. If others are fearful, there may be good reason for you to be fearful too."', '"Good,Fear,Reason"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"If one bird foraging in a flock on the ground suddenly takes off, all other birds will take off immediately after, before they even know what\'s going on. The one who stays behind may be prey."', '"Bird,Will,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Humans have a lot of pro-social tendencies.', '"Lot,Tendencies,Humans"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Male chimpanzees have an extraordinarily strong drive for dominance. They\'re constantly jockeying for position.', '"Drive,Position,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'The thinking is that we started evolving language not by speaking but by gesturing.', '"Thinking,Language,Evolving"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The role of inequity in society is grossly underestimated. Inequity is not good for your health, basically."', '"Health,Good,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Very ancient parts of the brain are involved in moral decision making.', '"Brain,Decision,Moral"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'There is little evidence that other animals judge the appropriateness of actions that do not directly affect themselves.', '"Judge,Animals,Evidence"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Chimps don\'t have language. Humans actively instruct others about how things should be done. Chimpanzees probably pick up cultural traditions by observation.', '"Done,Language,Observation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'There are beautiful examples of art done by chimpanzees in human care.', '"Art,Beautiful,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Science is not inherently good.', '"Science,Good,Inherently"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Sometimes I read about someone saying with great authority that animals have no intentions and no feelings, and I wonder, \'Doesn\'t this guy have a dog?\'"', '"Great,Feelings,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Chimpanzees, typically, kiss and embrace after fights. They first make eye contact from a distance to see the mood of the others. Then they approach and kiss and embrace."', '"Mood,Kiss,See"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"In Africa, we have the bush meat trade, which means that, on a very large scale, animals are being killed in the forests and sold in the cities as a luxury food."', '"Food,Africa,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'I think we need to start thinking about grounding our moral systems in our biology.', '"Thinking,Start,Biology"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Religions have a strong binding function and a cohesive element. They emphasize the primacy of the community as opposed to the individual, and they also help set one community apart from another that doesn\'t share their beliefs."', '"Community,Help,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The primate laugh is given in playful contexts, and as such has a strong similarity to the human laugh."', '"Laugh,Playful,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Understanding the need for religion is a far superior goal to bashing it.', '"Religion,Understanding,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"There are many reasons for kindness, and religion is just one of them."', '"Religion,Kindness,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"We need to separate the process of evolution - which is, indeed, a self-serving process - and the actual motivations of animals."', '"Process,Evolution,Indeed"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The more self-aware an animal is, the more empathetic it tends to be."', '"Animal,More,Empathetic"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Although elephants are far more distantly related to us than the great apes, they seem to have evolved similar social and cognitive capacities."', '"Great,More,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Male bonobos really don\'t fit the human male ideal.', '"Human,Ideal,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Exclusive homosexuality is not very common in nature.', '"Nature,Exclusive,Common"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Scientists are supposed to study animals in a totally objective fashion, similar to the way we inspect a rock or measure the circumference of a tree trunk. Emotions are not to interfere with the assessment. The animal-rights movement capitalizes on this perception, depicting scientists as devoid of compassion."', '"Emotions,Tree,Compassion"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"One thing bothered me as a student. In the 1960s, human behavior was totally off limits for the biologist. There was animal behavior, then there was a long time nothing, after which came human behavior as a totally separate category best left to a different group of scientists."', '"Best,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The intuitive connection children feel with animals can be a tremendous source of joy. The unconditional love received from pets, and the lack of artifice in the relationship, contrast sharply with the much trickier dealings with members of their own species."', '"Love,Relationship,Joy"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Experiments with animals have long been handicapped by our anthropocentric attitude: We often test them in ways that work fine with humans but not so well with other species.', '"Attitude,Work,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"I was born in Den Bosch, where the painter Hieronymus Bosch named himself after. And so I\'ve always been very fond of this painter who lived and worked in the 15th century."', '"Born,Always,I Was Born"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Future benefits rarely figure in the minds of animals.', '"Future,Animals,Minds"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'I was too restless as a boy to sit through an entire mass. It was akin to aversion training. I looked at it like a puppet show with a totally predictable story line. The only aspect I really liked was the music.', '"Music,Training,Boy"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', 'Dogmatists have one advantage: they are poor listeners.', '"Poor,Advantage,Listeners"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"Most exotic animals are not particularly interested in people, which makes it hard to provoke them. Human-rearing gets them used to and sometimes imprinted on humans, which makes them potentially dangerous."', '"People,Sometimes,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe86', '"The term \'alpha female\' originated in my field of animal behavior, but has acquired new meaning. It refers to women who are in charge, for example, by flirting and dating on their own terms. It is also used maliciously for a loud-mouthed, controlling woman who has no patience with deviating opinions."', '"Patience,Women,Dating"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'Biodiversity starts in the distant past and it points toward the future.', '"Future,Past,Biodiversity"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"I think a photograph, of whatever it might be - a landscape, a person - requires personal involvement. That means knowing your subject, not just snapping at what\'s in front of you."', '"Person,Landscape,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'Nature\'s my muse and it\'s been my passion.', '"Nature,Passion,Muse"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"A lion is not a lion is not a lion. As individuals, as mates, as members of a society, they\'re all very different."', '"Society,Lion,Members"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'Life needs a membrane to contain itself so it can replicate and mutate.', '"Life,Needs,Itself"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'Life is a force in its own right. It is a new element. And it has altered the Earth. It covers Earth like a skin.', '"Life,Skin,Life Is A"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"Tourism is important because it can create sustainable local economies. I\'d much rather have 1,000 tourists going up the Tambopata than 1,000 gold miners."', '"Gold,Important,Create"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"The Galapagos Islands provide a window on time. In a geologic sense, the islands are young, yet they appear ancient."', '"Time,Window,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"My wife says that I become different once I start to work with animals. My movements become different, my mood is different. It involves letting everything fall behind you, becoming intuitive in your dealings with wild creatures in a way that bypasses reason. Sometimes it\'s more like a dance than anything else."', '"Work,Wife,Mood"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'I want to interpret the natural world and our links to it. It\'s driven by the belief of many world-class scientists that we\'re in the midst of an extinction crisis... This time it\'s us that\'s doing it.', '"Time,World,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', 'I became interested in photography during my first visit to the United States. I was a student at a university in Holland. I was overwhelmed by the beauty of the American West. That was when I learned about the tradition of nature in American photography.', '"Beauty,Nature,American"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe84', '"Water is the key to life, but in frozen form, it is a latent force. And when it vanishes, Earth becomes Mars."', '"Life,Water,Earth"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Is wellbeing only economic growth? Only salaries? Or is wellbeing also being able to breathe clean air and drink clean water?', '"Water,Growth,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'We need to be able to answer not yesterday\'s challenges but to tomorrow\'s challenges.', '"Tomorrow,Challenges,Yesterday"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Respect for the rule of law is not optional; it\'s fundamental.', '"Respect,Law,Rule Of Law"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Nationalism makes us poor because its Siamese twin, protectionism, will destroy the internal market and disrupt international trade."', '"Will,Poor,Nationalism"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'The Netherlands believes in a vigorous Europe with a commission that is independent and robust.', '"Independent,Europe,Netherlands"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Nationalism is like alcoholism: a short period of exaltation followed by a long period of headaches.', '"Long,Nationalism,Short"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I am a huge fan of the Premier League, but do you think it will maintain its attractiveness if the Champions League is only an affair between English clubs and one or two others?"', '"I Am,Will,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Plastic waste is undeniably a big issue, and Europeans need to act together to tackle this problem because plastic waste ends up in our air, our soil, our oceans, and in our food."', '"Food,Together,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If Europe does not understand that our sister continent, Africa, a stone\'s throw away, is going to face a demographic explosion, if there is no real economic and political restructuring, if we do not understand we have a collective responsibility for Africa, there is not a fence high enough to stop people coming to Europe."', '"Political,Face,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If you believe that through putting the judiciary under political control you can make it a better judiciary, you are wrong, and you are violating your own obligations under European treaties."', '"Political,Believe,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The Treaty of Lisbon gave the European parliament a stronger role as co-legislator and the European Council its own president. Furthermore, the treaty introduced checks on subsidiarity - the concept that decisions should be taken as close as possible to the citizens - in an effort to cut back on unnecessary rules and regulations."', '"Effort,Rules,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If there\'s no future for Jews in Europe, there\'s no future for Europe."', '"Future,Europe,Jews"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"For me, arguably, the European Parliament is the best-functioning European institution. They are extremely good at law-making; they\'re extremely good at finding compromise under pressure."', '"Good,Me,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'The European Union is not unbreakable; something that is breakable is extremely valuable.', '"Valuable,European Union,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'The U.K. is leaving the E.U. but not Europe.', '"Leaving,Europe"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Public support will dwindle if the public thinks that free movement means undermining of social security systems... we need to get that right.', '"Free,Support,Security"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I want Europe to go forward, not backward."', '"Go,Europe,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Protectionism has never been an answer, will never be an answer. We need trade. We need trade agreements worldwide."', '"Will,Never,Answer"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The German car industry has a clear vision of the necessity of stability in the continent that goes beyond selling cars. For Germany, the economy is an instrument in a much wider issue of stability in continental Europe and overcoming the mistakes of the past."', '"Car,Vision,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Is it not in human nature sometimes, based on the facts that you now know, to reconsider?"', '"Nature,Facts,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'One of the principles upon which the E.U. is built is the separation of powers and the independence of the judiciary.', '"Independence,Principles,Judiciary"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Being part of the E.U. in Poland means that for the first time in a millennium, nobody disputes Poland\'s borders, and it brought a level of freedom that Poland has never known before."', '"Freedom,Time,First Time"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I think the E.U. means different things to different countries. In the U.K., traditionally, if you know anything about the U.K.\'s history and its relationship with the E.U., it is about the common market; it\'s about being part of something that is good for jobs and growth."', '"History,Relationship,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Europeans distrust a Europe that overpromises and underdelivers.', '"Europe,Distrust,Europeans"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"For all its shortcomings, European co-operation and integration has created an understanding of shared destiny. We no longer point guns at each other; we fight it out at a conference table. And we will continue to do so when the U.K. is no longer a member state but, I hope, still a friend."', '"Hope,Fight,Destiny"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Responsible politicians should never indulge in nostalgia - it is too much of a distraction at a time when a rapidly changing world throws up so many challenges, when we need to keep our wits about us."', '"Time,Challenges,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The main actors on the world stage are the size of continents, be they nation states or voluntary groupings of nation states such as the E.U. Nostalgia can help us ignore these harsh realities for a while, but it will not make them go away."', '"World,Nostalgia,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Since when is politics consistent?', '"Politics,Since,Consistent"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'I\'m just one generation between someone who cheered when Germans were burning and someone who doesn\'t even know that there is a border. That\'s a miracle - really is a miracle - and it gets me really emotional.', '"Me,Generation,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If the E.U. is to survive... it is based on the fact that for every community that belongs in Europe, there is a place in Europe."', '"Community,Place,Survive"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If children knew what the effects are of using single-use plastic straws for drinking sodas or whatever, they might reconsider and use paper straws or no straws at all."', '"Children,Whatever,Paper"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'How many millions of straws do we use every day across Europe? I would have people not use plastic straws any more.', '"Day,People,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Look at what the divisiveness of Brexit has done to the U.K.', '"Look,Done,Brexit"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'The absolute low point for me in more than 30 years of professional life was the Brexit vote.', '"Life,Me,Professional"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'I find it unspeakably sad that the United Kingdom has voted to leave the European Union.', '"Sad,Find,Leave"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I think in Trump\'s view of the world, when the other person loses, he wins."', '"View,World,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"As long as U.K. remains member of the E.U., it should respect the E.U. law."', '"Respect,Long,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"While, of course, you cannot discriminate between nationals of member states, access to the labour market does not mean automatic access to social security systems."', '"Security,Mean,Social"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Britain can get far better results if it engages with Europe than standing on the sidelines and saying that Europe should change.', '"Change,Better,Standing"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"There\'s a myth that in Arab countries, they all like Palestinians. They don\'t. On the contrary."', '"Myth,Like,On The Contrary"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The problem with UKIP and the extreme right - Mr. Le Pen, Wilders - they are really good at making an analysis of the problem. And they immediately go completely overboard in providing a solution that would never work and is morally completely unacceptable."', '"Work,Good,Pen"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Let\'s be clear: a nationalist is not a patriot.', '"Patriot,Clear,Nationalist"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"It has become routine for national politicians to blame Europe. When something works, they claim it as their success. When something doesn\'t work, then Europe is to blame."', '"Success,Work,Blame"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I\'m from Limburg, near the German border."', '"Border,Near,German"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"My parents married in 1959 and came to Amsterdam on honeymoon. That was a huge thing, event, for them. Now my children fly off for the weekend to Riga, Prague, or Barcelona."', '"Fly,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"This is the game of those who deny climate change or who deny the need for sustainability. They say, \'They are going to take everything away from us. They are going to take our cars away from us. They are going to take our steaks from us. They are going to take all the things that make life nice away from us. So let\'s not go there.\'"', '"Life,Change,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If we put our policies in the right order, we have a sustainable society without lowering but even increasing our levels of wellbeing."', '"Society,Right,Order"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If you want to maintain the unique character of our sport in Europe, which is of great importance to millions of people, you need to be able to put associations in a position to protect the weaker clubs."', '"Great,Character,Unique"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Given the amount of money circulating in the sport, European taxpayers and supporters are entitled to know how their clubs are being managed."', '"Money,Know,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'We need to wake up to idea that you cannot treat sport on equal terms with other parts of the economy.', '"Treat,Wake Up,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If we do not counter the argument that most radical nationlists use, which is, \'To protect is to be protectionist,\' if we don\'t counter that argument, all of our economies will suffer."', '"Will,Argument,Protect"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'I think we have a political and moral duty to do everything within our power to maintain the Good Friday Agreement.', '"Good,Power,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"We need a tough approach to make justice prevail and, also, because sports should not be damaged by the violence of hooligans."', '"Sports,Justice,Tough"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"It is a duty for any government to uphold the rule of law, and this sometimes requires the proportionate use of force."', '"Government,Law,Duty"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If the law does not give you what you want, you can oppose the law, you can work to change the law, but you cannot ignore the law. So it is fundamental that the constitutions of every one of our member states are upheld and respected."', '"Change,Work,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Whether they are Jewish, Muslim, Christian, or atheist, everybody has a place in this society."', '"Society,Atheist,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The argument that won the Brexit campaign is the one that said take back control... which is another way of saying we want to control our destinies again. This is an existential issue for the whole of Europe, not just for the U.K., because this sentiment is not limited to the United Kingdom."', '"Way,Control,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'The European Union should come up with a solid plan to help especially Poland and Slovakia make this transition away from coal.', '"Help,Plan,European Union"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'Our darkest angels in Europe are always somewhere under the surface.', '"Always,Darkest,Somewhere"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If you look at European societies since the financial crisis began in 2008, with very, very few exceptions, the differences between rich and poor have increased, and sometimes hugely."', '"Look,Rich,Differences"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"Nationalism makes us weak because its eternal seeking of enemies, its disdain of others, its need to feel superior makes cooperation with other nations to collectively guarantee our freedom and security much more difficult."', '"Freedom,Difficult,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If nationalism makes us poor, weak, and morally insecure, how can it claim to be patriotic? I maintain that nationalists are unpatriotic."', '"Poor,Nationalism,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"The issue of migration has played a key role in all of our member states, wherever we are. Only we, as a European Union, can convince our citizens that we do have an answer to this - not deny migration, not pretend you can solve it by building fences and walls, not pretending we can solve it by letting everybody in."', '"Building,Migration,Walls"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'What is the issue that has brought the European Union to the brink? The issue of migration.', '"Migration,European Union,Union"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"If you understand that we need a comprehensive approach to the migration issue, and only at European level, will this comprehensive approach be valuable and work. If we cannot convince our member states and citizens of that, then we will be in the same situation as the Dutch citizens were in 1581."', '"Work,Situation,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"In a free Europe... the system of power lies on three pillars. These are democracy, rule of law, and human rights. It\'s impossible to use one against the other."', '"Power,Democracy,Impossible"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', 'I believe many people - especially small- and medium-sized enterprises across the European Union - are disenchanted with Europe because we haven\'t delivered the goods.', '"Believe,People,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe85', '"I will do everything I can... to make sure that Poland sticks to a development that fosters the rule of law, democracy."', '"Democracy,Law,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Poor diet and sedentary behaviour have led to an increase in obesity and lifestyle-related disease and a huge rise in chronic medical conditions.', '"Medical,Diet,Rise"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Like all major transitions in human history, the shift from a linear to a circular economy will be a tumultuous one. It will feature heroes and pioneers, naysayers and obstacles, and moments of victory and doubt. If we persevere, however, we will put our economy back on a path of growth and sustainability."', '"History,Growth,Path"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Waste does not exist in nature because ecosystems reuse everything that grows in a never-ending cycle of efficiency and purpose.', '"Nature,Purpose,Efficiency"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Minimally invasive surgery is the way forward: the patient goes home the next day; there are fewer complications.', '"Home,Day,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"If we are to ensure that healthcare remains affordable and widely available for future generations, we need to radically rethink how we provide and manage it - in collaboration with key health system partners - and apply the technology that can help achieve these changes."', '"Health,Future,Technology"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We undertook a huge internal transformation to sharpen our customer focus, step up innovation, improve productivity to ensure competitiveness, change our culture, and simplify our ways of working so that our size and scale became a competitive advantage rather than a bureaucratic hangover after years of diversification."', '"Change,Focus,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Lumileds is a highly successful supplier of lighting components to the general illumination, automotive, and consumer electronics markets, with a strong customer base."', '"Strong,Customer,Consumer"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('399999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"At the core, Philips is an innovation company. And for innovation to work, you need to look for the unmet needs."', '"Work,Look,Innovation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Even though we live in a fast-changing world with short term-ism all around, it requires years of determination to transform a company and structurally reap the rewards. Innovation companies need to set their sights on solving unmet needs - but this approach requires focus and long-term tenacity."', '"Focus,World,Determination"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'The agreement to acquire Volcano significantly advances our strategy to become the leading systems integrator in image-guided therapies.', '"Strategy,Volcano,Become"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"In the Asian marketplace, we need to come out with products every nine months, not every two years."', '"Two,Need,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Genomics, Artificial Intelligence, and Deep Machine learning technologies are helping practitioners deliver better diagnosis and actually freeing up time for patient interaction."', '"Time,Learning,Intelligence"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"The global healthcare industry is undergoing a paradigm shift, providing significant opportunities for Philips to deliver more integrated solutions across the continuum of care - from prevention, diagnosis, and treatment to monitoring and aftercare."', '"Care,Healthcare,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"By innovating and investing in health technology, we believe that we can really change the future of health."', '"Change,Health,Future"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Light is one of the basic areas that will give you comfort, but it is undergoing a technological revolution in moving from conventional lighting to semiconductor-based lighting, and as it does that, it is becoming intelligent with the transition from analogue to digital."', '"Light,Comfort,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Government should seek more strategic approaches to developing dynamic, resilient infrastructure. Business must be more creative in offering financing solutions as partners with government, and people must support sustainable innovation as a public policy priority."', '"Business,Government,Support"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'I am pleased with the response of investors towards Philips Lighting and the successful pricing of the I.P.O. This strategic milestone will allow Royal Philips to focus on the fast-growing health technology market.', '"Health,Technology,Focus"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'It is vital that a company\'s culture shows a willingness to invest in employee wellbeing with no stigma or penalty attached to prioritising good health.', '"Health,Good,Good Health"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Healthcare is a conservative marketplace.', '"Healthcare,Conservative,Marketplace"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"In Kenya, e-learning has taught 12,000 nurses how to treat major diseases such as HIV and malaria, compared to the 100 nurses a year that can be taught in a classroom."', '"Treat,Classroom,HIV"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Should one of your employees have a physical or mental health problem, I would argue that it is as much something for the employer as the individual to contend with."', '"Health,Your,Mental Health"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Compassion, together with contractual responsibility for one\'s workforce, is a mark of a top employer."', '"Together,Responsibility,Compassion"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Employers can assist employees in looking after their health by giving guidance on energy management, sleep and healthy eating, working relationships, and helping maintain a sense of purpose at work."', '"Work,Health,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'What Philips has to offer to India is to further enhance the state of healthcare for the over billion people in this country.', '"People,Country,Healthcare"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Certain product categories become less attractive for us because, as they become mature, they become low-cost, and hence, there is less to invent. There is less to invent in a television, whereas in heath technology, there is a lot to invent. So we wanted to put our innovative power to work where it really matters."', '"Work,Power,Technology"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"If we can keep you healthy, that is better. If you fall sick, you go to the hospital. Both sides, Philips is present."', '"Hospital,Better,Fall"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Our health underpins our happiness and is a foundation of economic advancement.', '"Happiness,Health,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"First and foremost, we must take a more holistic view of patient care journeys and then better integrate workflows and technology so that the care experience is seamless and provided at the location where it makes most sense."', '"Experience,Technology,View"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Engagement with young people is always a refreshing break with routine. It\'s also a reminder of how we need to constantly keep our thinking agile and unencumbered by traditional rules.', '"Thinking,Refreshing,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'We knew we could put the company on the right side of history by decisive transformative action and by redefining our purpose to improving people\'s lives through innovation.', '"History,Purpose,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Indeed, the Fourth Industrial Revolution will greatly lead to increased consumer health awareness and self-management and will enable individualized treatment pathways supported by tele-health care and coaching."', '"Health,Awareness,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Thanks to the digital and big data revolution, we can start to do what was previously unthinkable - to improve patient outcomes and lower healthcare costs while delivering personalized care to each individual."', '"Care,Start,Digital"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Healthcare continues to move outside the hospital and into our homes and everyday lives. With leading doctors and psychologists, for example, we\'ve developed personal health programs designed around patients to catalyze sustainable behavioural change."', '"Change,Health,Hospital"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Growing and aging populations are putting increased pressure on health-care systems that are already buckling under the burden of chronic diseases like cancer and diabetes.', '"Pressure,Diabetes,Aging"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"If we are to ensure that health care remains affordable and widely available for future generations, we need to rethink radically how we provide and manage it."', '"Health,Future,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Crucially, healthcare needs to become connected. It should become effortless for medical professionals to share relevant data with colleagues around the world. Medical devices and systems in hospitals should be able to combine multiple sources of information."', '"Medical,Colleagues,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"With access to professional coaching and support around the clock, patients will feel more empowered to manage their own physical wellbeing."', '"Support,Feel,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Perhaps sooner than we think, African innovations will help the rest of the world create lasting social and economic value."', '"World,Value,Rest"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Our myopic focus on producing and consuming as cheaply as possible has created a linear economy in which objects are briefly used and then discarded as waste.', '"Focus,Possible,Waste"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Philips is committed to the circular economy and is applying its principles throughout the organization. We are redesigning our products and looking at ways to capture their residual value.', '"Value,Looking,Organization"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Government should create the environment and incentives to stimulate investment in sustainable innovation, take away barriers, and accelerate adoption, even in turbulent economic times."', '"Government,Innovation,Investment"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Changing the ways of governments usually doesn\'t happen quickly, but time is a luxury the world no longer enjoys."', '"Time,World,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Time may not be on our side, but innovation is."', '"Time,Innovation,Side"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"As humans, we\'ve always innovated our way out of problems, whether it was the first torch to light a dark cave or the steam engine that sparked a revolution."', '"Light,Problems,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"City farming is not only possible, it is the very definition of the kind of meaningful, sustainable innovation we will need to meet the grand challenges of the 21st century: climate change; population growth; ageing population; urbanization; rising demand for energy, food and water; poverty; and access to healthcare."', '"Change,Food,Water"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Meaningful innovation can be an important catalyst in encouraging resilience in seniors, keeping them independent and engaged."', '"Important,Innovation,Independent"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Sustainable solutions based on innovation can create a more resilient world only if that innovation is focused on the health and well-being of its inhabitants. And it is at that point - where technology and human needs intersect - that we will find meaningful innovation.', '"Health,Technology,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Insurers reimburse critical care, not the avoidance of incidents. Therefore, investments are not targeted towards prevention."', '"Care,Prevention,Critical"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Concerns about the possible side-effects of connected care are swept aside by the expectations of the benefits when people are confronted with a chronic disease themselves. Resistance that could be privacy-related completely disappears.', '"Expectations,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'I remain convinced of the compelling case for connected care.', '"Care,Connected,Convinced"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Tech can help population health, make health more accessible, more affordable. Tech can also get people get more included in the economy and contribute and drive growth, and growth and wealth are great contributors to a safer world."', '"Health,Great,Growth"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"When I became CEO, I was really worried that we were in commoditized segments that were mature and no longer growing. So we made a radical pivot into health technology because that is one of the world\'s unmet needs."', '"Health,Technology,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Our strategy is focused on driving better outcomes for patients and higher productivity for hospitals.', '"Better,Strategy,Driving"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'It has not escaped us that other competitors have also identified health as an attractive marketplace.', '"Health,Attractive,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"When you make a courageous statement, people start to follow you, and that\'s nice."', '"People,Start,Follow"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Having a consumer brand helps us a lot. We will see more ambulatory care, and there will be a lot of new ways to deliver healthcare... and that means consumerism is going to play a bigger role."', '"Care,New,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Great companies need to reinvent themselves. We can do that: we can stay relevant, we can grow, and we can stay successful. It takes courage, but it\'s a path we\'ve been preparing for carefully."', '"Courage,Great,Path"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'The entire dynamics of the lighting market are changing. Value is moving toward systems and services.', '"Value,Moving,Lighting"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We are very optimistic about our opportunities in China. Our toothbrushes continue to sell very well, while the growth of private hospitals diminishes the risk of government preferring domestic suppliers."', '"Government,Growth,Continue"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'The conventional way of selling products out of the catalogue no longer works; the relationship needs to become more sticky.', '"Relationship,Way,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"In an aging world with more chronic disease, health and healthcare are enormous opportunities that we want to focus on."', '"Health,Focus,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We typically sell a catheter lab to a hospital, and it sits there for the next 10 years, and we don\'t visit the cardiologist on a daily basis. Volcano have a disposable business. They are in the cath lab on a daily basis."', '"Business,Daily,Hospital"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'There\'s much unlocked potential in Philips.', '"Potential,Much,Unlocked"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'You can\'t have a single design for all cities. The look and feel of the streetlights are very important.', '"Design,Look,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"I think, going forward, we need to be much more modest on expectations with regard to China growth: That\'s just being realistic."', '"Growth,Expectations,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"You need to dismount when your horse is dead. What was relevant 20 years ago is no longer relevant today. Therefore, you need to reinvent yourself."', '"Today,Yourself,Dead"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We can only compete in the world against competitors from Asia, the United States, or wherever if we look at unmet needs."', '"Look,World,Wherever"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"I think of the world as geographical regions, and it excites me to think about the opportunity that Europe can have if we consider it to be the 500-million-people region that it is."', '"Opportunity,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We can squabble between the siblings in Europe and not be very productive and then see China and the U.S. win over the European region. Or - and this is my preferred choice - we team up together and are the strong region that we want to be, using each others\' strengths and building on our commonalities to become the smartest region in the world."', '"Together,World,Choice"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'The traditional way that society looks at healthcare is to let people get terribly sick and then have an emergency room to take care of them and spend a lot of money on acute care for people who would have been kept out of hospital in the first place if they had had a lifestyle change.', '"Change,Money,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We invented television and stuck with it for 50 years, and then I decided to get out of that. I would like people to know that we are broader than consumer electronics."', '"People,Know,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We have transformed Philips into a focused leader in health technology, delivering innovation to help people manage their health."', '"Health,Technology,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"To become the global leader in HealthTech and shape the future of the industry, we will combine our vibrant Healthcare and Consumer Lifestyle businesses into one company."', '"Future,Lifestyle,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Philips is uniquely positioned to help reshape and optimize population health management by leveraging big data and delivering care across the health continuum, from healthy living and prevention to diagnosis, minimally invasive treatment, recovery, and home care."', '"Health,Home,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'A siloed approach between suppliers doesn\'t really help hospitals well enough.', '"Help,Enough,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"The computer can do a much better job than the human eye, as it is much more systematic in analysing tissues."', '"Better,Job,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'I\'ve always flagged that it will take some time to gradually sell down our interest in lighting and basically pivot to be a medtech company focused entirely on health technology.', '"Health,Time,Technology"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"The shift in demand is toward partners that can improve productivity, and in part, that can be done by software."', '"Done,Software,Demand"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"Price erosion in components is quite fast. If you can capitalize on that by bringing products to the market faster, you will actually gain a better margin realization."', '"Better,Will,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We are addressing duplication and complexity. At the same time, we are investing more in research and development, speeding up the time to market of new innovations, and expanding our sales force in markets where growth is to be found, like Turkey, Russia, the Mideast, China, and southeast Asia."', '"Time,Growth,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Healthy people are not very motivated to manage their health. They just don\'t care.', '"Health,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"When you try to master the emotions of a decision and say, if you\'re 50 years from now and you look back, \'Did we take the right decisions?\' Then the decision becomes a lot easier."', '"Look,Decision,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"In the back of my mind was the nagging discussion: where do we take the portfolio? You can get rid of TV, fine, but then you are in lighting and in health, and those don\'t have a lot to do with each other."', '"Health,Mind,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"I came back to Philips and quickly realised that the TV business had a major performance issue and some structural challenges. Rather than try to tweak it and sit things out, we said we had to go for a structural solution."', '"Business,Challenges,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We started experimenting with television in 1928. For a lot of people, Philips has a lot to do with TV."', '"People,Television,Started"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Sometimes that Dutch consensus approach doesn\'t move you forward fast enough.', '"Sometimes,Fast,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', 'Health care has to be delivered as an integrated service across the entire continuum of care. This runs from healthy living and prevention to diagnosis and treatment and recovery and homecare.', '"Health,Service,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"How can we keep people healthy, and if they get sick, how can we treat them right the first time?"', '"Time,Treat,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"As soon as a disease is diagnosed, we still need someone to deliver the care."', '"Care,Someone,Disease"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"If we are going to get a grip on escalating costs, we have to focus more on prevention rather than acute care. Technology can help us do that."', '"Technology,Focus,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe87', '"We can\'t think in terms of designing products that we throw over the wall to customers, but instead, we need to design products that are upgradable and maintainable and that can be mined for materials and components that can be reused."', '"Design,Need,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', 'For the black man there is only one destiny. And it is white.', '"Black,Man,Destiny"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', 'Fervor is the weapon of choice of the impotent.', '"Choice,Weapon,Fervor"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', 'He who is reluctant to recognize me opposes me.', '"Me,He,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', 'Violence is man re-creating himself.', '"Man,Violence,Himself"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', '"I ascribe a basic importance to the phenomenon of language. To speak means to be in a position to use a certain syntax, to grasp the morphology of this or that language, but it means above all to assume a culture, to support the weight of a civilization."', '"Culture,Support,Language"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', '"However painful it may be for me to accept this conclusion, I am obliged to state it: for the black man there is only one destiny. And it is white."', '"Black,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe88', 'There is a point at which methods devour themselves.', '"Point,Which,Themselves"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"German football is like English football. The Germans and the English do not play like a Brazilian side. They have to improve, bring up their young players, who have character."', '"Football,Character,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"At least six Bayern players, who have won almost everything, are in the national squad."', '"Everything,Squad,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', 'Certainly it is a different world for players nowadays. But it depends on the individual.', '"World,Players,Depends"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"For example, Michael Jordan earns $100million a year but continues to play basketball and remains a modest human being."', '"Human,Human Being,Michael Jordan"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"Since Sven Goran Eriksson took over, England have been fantastic."', '"Over,England,Fantastic"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', 'We should not fool ourselves. We are not one of the world\'s top teams any more.', '"Fool,World,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"At any rate, I can only see such a success having positive effects for everyone, particularly as our anticipation of the World cup would only increase further."', '"Positive,Success,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"The most important thing however is the money. What use would it be to us, to have a a mighty stadium but a useless team, because we couldn\'t afford anything better?"', '"Money,Better,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"At the World Cup and even now at the Confederations Cup, our security provisions will ensure the greatest level of protection possible for all those participating - both inside and outside the stadiums."', '"World,Security,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"Back then, a half-a-century ago, the situation was totally different. Economically, we were practically on our knees, and politically, we were still excluded from the community of nations. Today, in this respect, we have a totally different and much more stable basis."', '"Respect,Today,Community"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"It would make me a lot happier if I could meet up again next year with as many friends as possible from all over the world who I\'ve met during my career. That\'s where the great opportunity lies, for me personally, in our role as World Cup host."', '"Great,Opportunity,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', 'The Olympic stadium may have been built only in the early 1970s but it was clear for a long time it had no future. For many reasons it is not good enough for modern football and today\'s fans.', '"Future,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"The trouble for today\'s footballers is they have too many distractions. We used to get our old players coming to watch training with football magazines in their hands. Now, more often than not, they are checking the share prices."', '"Today,Football,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"The two designs are completely different. The first is totally futuristic, the second is more classical. You can of course get very excited about doing something completely out of the ordinary, just like the Olympic stadium in its time. But each to his or her own taste."', '"Time,Doing,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"The World Cup tournament overall and, naturally, the new stadiums at its heart, are the ideal platform to portray Germany as a positive and exceptional location, and above all of course, as a highly capable economic location."', '"Positive,Heart,World"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"We are the last remaining country to allow ourselves two breaks in the season. You just have to look at England, Italy and Spain, they play right through the season. We on the other hand take six weeks off in the winter until the end of January, and that is a luxury."', '"Look,Country,End"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"In the World Cup, much depends for every team on how it develops during the tournament. There are always rising tensions. They come from within, and they come from the media."', '"World,Media,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"I kept my speeches short as captain. I focused on the key points of the opposition of the day. As coach, I was never afraid to give long speeches to the players throughout our preparations. It was important they had all the information possible."', '"Long,Day,Information"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"Rugby is a different game. There is an interruption every two minutes also in American football. Our soccer is a moving game: play, play, play, move, move - you don\'t interrupt."', '"Football,Game,American"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe89', '"If a Middle Eastern sheikh comes to buy Bayern Munich, he could buy 49 per cent. Fifty-one per cent must stay in Germany with the club. That law came about because of the developments of international football."', '"Football,Law,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"If we were to select the most intelligent, imaginative, energetic, and emotionally stable third of mankind, all races would be present."', '"Equality,Intelligent,Present"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"It is our task to inquire into the causes that have brought about the observed differentiation, and to investigate the sequence of events that have led to the establishment of the multifarious forms of human life."', '"Life,Task,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"Furthermore, the study of the present surroundings is insufficient: the history of the people, the influence of the regions through which it has passed on its migrations, and the people with whom it came into contact, must be considered."', '"History,Influence,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"Remember that in every single case in history the process of adaptation has been one of exceeding slowness. Do not look for the impossible, but do not let your path deviate from the quiet and steadfast insistence on full opportunities for your powers."', '"History,Path,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', 'The historical development of the work of anthropologists seems to single out clearly a domain of knowledge that heretofore has not been treated by any other science.', '"Work,Science,Knowledge"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"In other words, we are interested in the anatomical and mental characteristics of men living under the same biological, geographical, and social environment, and as determined by their past."', '"Men,Past,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"This idea was also brought out very clearly by Wallace, who emphasized that apparently reasonable activities of man might very well have developed without an actual application of reasoning."', '"Man,Well,Reasoning"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', 'Not so the scientist. The very essence of his life is the service of truth.', '"Life,Truth,Service"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', 'The disease of mutual distrust among nations is the bane of modern civilization.', '"Disease,Civilization,Distrust"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"I object to teaching of slogans intended to befog the mind, of whatever kind they may be."', '"Mind,Whatever,May"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"In France, that let down the barriers more than a hundred years ago, the feeling of antipathy is still strong enough to sustain an anti-Jewish political party."', '"Political,Enough,Political Party"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"We all know scientists who in private life do not come up to the standard of truthfulness, but who, nevertheless, would not consciously falsify the results of their researches."', '"Life,Private Life,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"We do not discuss the anatomical, physiological, and mental characteristics of man considered as an individual; but we are interested in the diversity of these traits in groups of men found in different geographical areas and in different social classes."', '"Men,Man,Diversity"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"My father had retained an emotional affection for the ceremonial of his parental home, without allowing it to influence his intellectual freedom."', '"Freedom,Home,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', 'My parents had broken through the shackles of dogma.', '"Parents,Broken,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8a', '"I hope I may have succeeded in presenting to you, however imperfectly, the currents of thought due to the work of the immortal Darwin which have helped to make anthropology what it is at the present time."', '"Work,Hope,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8b', '"I\'d really love to check out medieval times. I\'m obsessed with that kind of stuff, like on a horseback with a sword."', '"Love,Sword,Check"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8b', '"Changes can be made. New decisions can be made. If people say, \'It\'s not like that in the comics!\' Well, comic books reinvent their characters a lot. They do different things with them all the time. They\'re always changing, always keeping things fresh. So that shouldn\'t be an issue if the race changes for a character."', '"Time,Character,New"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8b', '"I\'m always trying to play pranks on people and doing silliness, singing extremely badly and extremely loudly on set."', '"Singing,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8b', '"There is a very diverse range of superheroes, especially with the Firestorm character. In the comics, there is a black Firestorm. But we still don\'t see that many black superheroes. So what The CW is doing and what DC Comics is doing with this whole universe with diversity is absolutely amazing."', '"Amazing,Black,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"The uneducated person perceives only the individual phenomenon, the partly educated person the rule, and the educated person the exception."', '"Person,Educated,Uneducated"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Drink and be thankful to the host! What seems insignificant when you have it, is important when you need it."', '"Thankful,Thanksgiving,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Those who want to row on the ocean of human knowledge do not get far, and the storm drives those out of their course who set sail."', '"Knowledge,Storm,Ocean"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'Prose talks and poetry sings.', '"Poetry,Prose,Sings"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Mankind is getting smarter every day. Actually, it only seems so. At least we are making progress. We\'re progressing, to be sure, ever more deeply into the forest."', '"Progress,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"To test a modest man\'s modesty do not investigate if he ignores applause, find out if he abides criticism."', '"Man,Criticism,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Without a notion of the transcendental, human beings would, indeed, be animals; however, only fools can be convinced of it, and only degenerates need such a conviction."', '"Indeed,Human,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"To declaim freedom verses seems like a poem within a poem; freedom requires guns, it requires arms, but no feet."', '"Freedom,Feet,Guns"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Science and art, or by the same token, poetry and prose differ from one another like a journey and an excursion. The purpose of the journey is its goal, the purpose of an excursion is the process."', '"Science,Art,Poetry"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'No shortcomings of other people cause us to be more intolerant than those which are caricatures of our own.', '"People,Own,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'The ideas of an age are most abundant where they are not crowded by original ideas.', '"Age,Ideas,Crowded"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"When the theater gates open, a mob pours inside, and it is the poet\'s task to turn it into an audience."', '"Task,Open,Inside"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Although your knowledge is weak and small, you need not be silent: since you cannot be judges be at least witnesses."', '"Knowledge,Your,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"If someone were to think that trees are made to support the sky, they would all seem too short."', '"Sky,Support,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Genius unrefined resembles a flash of lightning, but wisdom is like the sun."', '"Wisdom,Sun,Genius"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"No one will stop to help you when you are in need, but everyone forces opinions upon you that you do not require."', '"Will,Help,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Poetry, it is often said and loudly so, is life\'s true mirror. But a monkey looking into a work of literature looks in vain for Socrates."', '"Life,Work,Poetry"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"This searching and doubting and vacillating where nothing is clear but the arrogance of quest. I, too, had such noble ideas when I was still a boy."', '"Arrogance,Nothing,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'It\'s the misfortune of German authors that not a single one of them dares to expose his true character. Everyone thinks that he has to be better than he is.', '"Character,Better,True"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"You even called me stupid in your verse, and I\'m almost agreeing, for where stupidity is involved, you are quite an expert, friend."', '"Stupid,Stupidity,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Whoever places his trust into a system will soon be without a home. While you are building your third story, the two lower ones have already been dismantled."', '"Trust,Home,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'I look around me and nowhere do I see a stamp of disapproval with which nature marked a woman\'s candid brow.', '"Nature,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"Before passing different laws for different people, I\'d relinquish myself unto you as your slave."', '"Myself,People,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'Ideas are not thoughts; the thought respects the boundaries that the idea ignores thereby failing to realize itself.', '"Thoughts,Ideas,Realize"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"There shall be no slave in your home, male or female: Least of all the mother of your son."', '"Home,Son,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"The main reason why men and women make different aesthetic judgments is the fact that the latter, generally incapable of abstraction, only admire what meets their complete approval."', '"Women,Men,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', '"If we notice a few errors in the work of a proven master, we may and even will often be correct; if we believe, however, that he is completely and utterly mistaken, we are in danger of missing his entire concept."', '"Work,Believe,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8c', 'Progress will always have as its recourse to exaggerate what it cannot surpass.', '"Progress,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"You do not need to leave your room. Remain sitting at your table and listen. Do not even listen, simply wait, be quiet still and solitary. The world will freely offer itself to you to be unmasked, it has no choice, it will roll in ecstasy at your feet."', '"World,Feet,Wait"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Anyone who keeps the ability to see beauty never grows old.', '"Beauty,See,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Start with what is right rather than what is acceptable.', '"Wisdom,Start,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"In the fight between you and the world, back the world."', '"Fight,World,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Youth is happy because it has the ability to see beauty. Anyone who keeps the ability to see beauty never grows old.', '"Beauty,Youth,See"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"So long as you have food in your mouth, you have solved all questions for the time being."', '"Time,Food,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Every revolution evaporates and leaves behind only the slime of a new bureaucracy.', '"New,Revolution,Bureaucracy"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"He who seeks does not find, but he who does not seek will be found."', '"Will,Find,He"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Evil is whatever distracts.', '"Evil,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"God gives the nuts, but he does not crack them."', '"God,Brainy,Nuts"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"You can hold yourself back from the sufferings of the world, that is something you are free to do and it accords with your nature, but perhaps this very holding back is the one suffering you could avoid."', '"Nature,World,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"By believing passionately in something that still does not exist, we create it. The nonexistent is whatever we have not sufficiently desired."', '"Create,Whatever,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"It is not necessary that you leave the house. Remain at your table and listen. Do not even listen, only wait. Do not even wait, be wholly still and alone. The world will present itself to you for its unmasking, it can do no other, in ecstasy it will writhe at your feet."', '"Alone,World,Feet"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'A first sign of the beginning of understanding is the wish to die.', '"Die,Beginning,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Productivity is being able to do things that you were never able to do before.', '"Never,Things,Able"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'It is often safer to be in chains than to be free.', '"Free,Chains,Often"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"There are only two things. Truth and lies. Truth is indivisible, hence it cannot recognize itself; anyone who wants to recognize it has to be a lie."', '"Truth,Lie,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'From a certain point onward there is no longer any turning back. That is the point that must be reached.', '"Back,Point,Onward"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Atlas was permitted the opinion that he was at liberty, if he wished, to drop the Earth and creep away; but this opinion was all that he was permitted."', '"Liberty,Earth,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'One of the first signs of the beginning of understanding is the wish to die.', '"Die,Beginning,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"My peers, lately, have found companionship through means of intoxication - it makes them sociable. I, however, cannot force myself to use drugs to cheat on my loneliness - it is all that I have - and when the drugs and alcohol dissipate, will be all that my peers have as well."', '"Myself,Loneliness,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The indestructible is one: it is each individual human being and, at the same time, it is common to all, hence the incomparably indivisible union that exists between human beings."', '"Time,Human,Human Being"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The mediation by the serpent was necessary. Evil can seduce man, but cannot become man."', '"Man,Evil,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'I have the true feeling of myself only when I am unbearably unhappy.', '"Myself,I Am,True"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"My \'fear\' is my substance, and probably the best part of me."', '"Best,Fear,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Idleness is the beginning of all vice, the crown of all virtues."', '"Beginning,Virtues,Crown"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'One advantage in keeping a diary is that you become aware with reassuring clarity of the changes which you constantly suffer.', '"Diary,Clarity,Become"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'May I kiss you then? On this miserable paper? I might as well open the window and kiss the night air.', '"Night,Window,Kiss"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Suffering is the positive element in this world, indeed it is the only link between this world and the positive."', '"Positive,World,Suffering"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Don\'t despair, not even over the fact that you don\'t despair."', '"Despair,Over,Even"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'I do not read advertisements. I would spend all of my time wanting things.', '"Time,Things,My Time"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"In theory there is a possibility of perfect happiness: To believe in the indestructible element within one, and not to strive towards it."', '"Happiness,Believe,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'A book must be the ax for the frozen sea within us.', '"Sea,Us,Book"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Believing in progress does not mean believing that any progress has yet been made.', '"Progress,Mean,Believing"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"There is nothing besides a spiritual world; what we call the world of the senses is the Evil in the spiritual world, and what we call Evil is only the necessity of a moment in our eternal evolution."', '"Moment,World,Spiritual"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'The spirit becomes free only when it ceases to be a support.', '"Free,Support,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'In the struggle between yourself and the world second the world.', '"Struggle,World,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'No sooner said than done - so acts your man of worth.', '"Man,Done,Worth"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"We are separated from God on two sides; the Fall separates us from Him, the Tree of Life separates Him from us."', '"Life,God,Tree"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'A book should serve as the ax for the frozen sea within us.', '"Sea,Us,Serve"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Association with human beings lures one into self-observation.', '"Human,Association,Human Beings"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Don Quixote\'s misfortune is not his imagination, but Sancho Panza."', '"Imagination,Misfortune,His"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Anyone who cannot come to terms with his life while he is alive needs one hand to ward off a little his despair over his fate... but with his other hand he can note down what he sees among the ruins.', '"Life,Alive,Fate"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Hesitation before birth. If there is a transmigration of souls then I am not yet on the bottom rung. My life is a hesitation before birth.', '"Life,I Am,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'My guiding principle is this: Guilt is never to be doubted.', '"Guilt,Never,Principle"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"A stair not worn hollow by footsteps is, regarded from its own point of view, only a boring something made of wood."', '"View,Boring,Wood"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"If I shall exist eternally, how shall I exist tomorrow?"', '"Tomorrow,Exist,How"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Woman, or more precisely put, perhaps, marriage, is the representative of life with which you are meant to come to terms."', '"Life,Marriage,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"If it had been possible to build the Tower of Babel without climbing it, it would have been permitted."', '"Possible,Build,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"One must not cheat anyone, not even the world of its victory."', '"World,Victory,Must"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The decisive moment in human evolution is perpetual. That is why the revolutionary spiritual movements that declare all former things worthless are in the right, for nothing has yet happened."', '"Moment,Spiritual,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"By imposing too great a responsibility, or rather, all responsibility, on yourself, you crush yourself."', '"Great,Responsibility,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Religions get lost as people do.', '"Lost,People,Religions"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Dread of night. Dread of not-night.', '"Night,Dread"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"How pathetically scanty my self-knowledge is compared with, say, my knowledge of my room. There is no such thing as observation of the inner world, as there is of the outer world."', '"Knowledge,World,Observation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"We are sinful not only because we have eaten of the Tree of Knowledge, but also because we have not yet eaten of the Tree of Life. The state in which we are is sinful, irrespective of guilt."', '"Life,Knowledge,Tree"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Let me remind you of the old maxim: people under suspicion are better moving than at rest, since at rest they may be sitting in the balance without knowing it, being weighed together with their sins."', '"Together,Me,Balance"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Not everyone can see the truth, but he can be it."', '"Truth,See,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'The history of mankind is the instant between two strides taken by a traveler.', '"History,Two,Mankind"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"It is only our conception of time that makes us call the Last Judgement by this name. It is, in fact, a kind of martial law."', '"Time,Law,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"We all have wings, but they have not been of any avail to us and if we could tear them off, we would do so."', '"Wings,Us,Avail"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'In a certain sense the Good is comfortless.', '"Good,Sense,Certain"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Test yourself on mankind. It is something that makes the doubter doubt, the believer believe."', '"Believe,Yourself,Doubt"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'The thornbush is the old obstacle in the road. It must catch fire if you want to go further.', '"Fire,Road,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Always first draw fresh breath after outbursts of vanity and complacency.', '"Complacency,Always,Fresh"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Self-control means wanting to be effective at some random point in the infinite radiations of my spiritual existence.', '"Random,Spiritual,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"In argument similes are like songs in love; they describe much, but prove nothing."', '"Love,Nothing,Argument"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The Bible is a sanctum; the world, sputum."', '"World,Bible"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'Writers speak stench.', '"Speak,Writers"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The experience of life consists of the experience which the spirit has of itself in matter and as matter, in mind and as mind, in emotion, as emotion, etc."', '"Life,Experience,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'The fact that our task is exactly commensurate with our life gives it the appearance of being infinite.', '"Life,Appearance,Task"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Heaven is dumb, echoing only the dumb."', '"Dumb,Heaven,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'It is comforting to reflect that the disproportion of things in the world seems to be only arithmetical.', '"World,Reflect,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'If there is a transmigration of souls then I am not yet on the bottom rung. My life is a hesitation before birth.', '"Life,I Am,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Sensual love deceives one as to the nature of heavenly love; it could not do so alone, but since it unconsciously has the element of heavenly love within it, it can do so."', '"Love,Alone,Nature"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Tyranny or slavery, born of selfishness, are the two educational methods of parents; all gradations of tyranny or slavery."', '"Parents,Tyranny,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', 'How can one take delight in the world unless one flees to it for refuge?', '"World,Delight,Take"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"The relationship to one\'s fellow man is the relationship of prayer, the relationship to oneself is the relationship of striving; it is from prayer that one draws the strength for one\'s striving."', '"Strength,Relationship,Prayer"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Hiding places there are innumerable, escape is only one, but possibilities of escape, again, are as many as hiding places."', '"Escape,Possibilities,Places"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"Martyrs do not underrate the body, they allow it to be elevated on the cross. In this they are at one with their antagonists."', '"Body,Cross,Martyrs"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8d', '"One tells as few lies as possible only by telling as few lies as possible, and not by having the least possible opportunity to do so."', '"Opportunity,Possible,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8e', '"The final test of a painting, theirs, mine, any other, is: does the painter\'s emotions come across?"', '"Painting,Emotions,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8e', '"If you\'re a painter, you\'re not alone. There\'s no way to be alone."', '"Alone,Way,Painter"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8e', 'The nature of anguish is translated into different forms.', '"Nature,Different,Anguish"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'Beware of missing chances; otherwise it may be altogether too late some day.', '"Chance,Day,Late"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Life is only a long and bitter suicide, and faith alone can transform this suicide into a sacrifice."', '"Life,Alone,Faith"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'Mournful and yet grand is the destiny of the artist.', '"Art,Destiny,Artist"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Music embodies feeling without forcing it to contend and combine with thought, as it is forced in most arts and especially in the art of words."', '"Art,Music,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'Truth is a great flirt.', '"Truth,Great,Truth Is"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'The character of instrumental music... lets the emotions radiate and shine in their own character without presuming to display them as real or imaginary representations.', '"Music,Character,Emotions"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Brahms\' Variations are better than mine, but mine were written before his."', '"Better,Mine,Before"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Real men are sadly lacking in this world, for when they are put to the test they prove worthless."', '"Men,World,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'It is impossible to imagine a more complete fusion with nature than that of the Gypsy.', '"Nature,Impossible,More"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'A person of any mental quality has ideas of his own. This is common sense.', '"Quality,Ideas,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Inspiration is enough to give expression to the tone in singing, especially when the song is without words."', '"Song,Singing,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'It is my fervent wish and my greatest ambition to leave a work with a few useful instructions for the pianists after me.', '"Work,Me,Ambition"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Companions, in misery and worse, that is what we all are, and to try to change this substantially avails us nothing."', '"Change,Nothing,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Broad paths are open to every endeavour, and a sympathetic recognition is assured to every one who consecrates his art to the divine services of a conviction of a consciousness."', '"Art,Divine,Recognition"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"I find little in the works of Beethoven, Berlioz, Wagner and others when they are led by a conductor who functions like a windmill."', '"Find,Others,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'Sorrowful and great is the artist\'s destiny.', '"Great,Destiny,Artist"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"I conclude that the Wagnerian operas which are already in the repertoire, and other masterworks as well, stand in no further need of my services."', '"Stand,Well,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'I foster a sorrowful conception of affection. Make no sacrifices.', '"Affection,Make,Conception"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Without any assistance whatever, I founded a school in Weimar in 10 years. Only I could perform certain works with the scanty means that I dared not ask anyone else to work with."', '"Work,School,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'The public is always good.', '"Good,Always,Public"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"I did not compose my work as one might put on a church vestment... rather it sprung from the truly fervent faith of my heart, such as I have felt it since my childhood."', '"Work,Faith,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"As the mother teaches her children how to express themselves in their language, so one Gypsy musician teaches the other. They have never shown any need for notation."', '"Children,Language,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"A theatre receives recognition through its initiative, which is indispensable for first-rate performances."', '"Recognition,Through,Theatre"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"The music of the Gypsies belongs in the sphere of improvisation rather than in any other, without which it would have no power to exist."', '"Power,Music,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"Supreme serenity still remains the Ideal of great Art. The shapes and transitory forms of life are but stages toward this Ideal, which Christ\'s religion illuminates with His divine light."', '"Life,Art,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"In Hungary all native music, in its origin, is divided naturally into melody destined for song or melody for the dance."', '"Music,Song,Dance"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', 'We need improvement in the style of performance. There is no more advantage in a musician who plays and conducts than in one who is only a beater of rhythm.', '"Improvement,Style,Performance"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe8f', '"The principal task of a conductor is not to put himself in evidence but to disappear behind his functions as much as possible. We are pilots, not servants."', '"Principal,Possible,Task"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', '"Today we are searching for things in nature that are hidden behind the veil of appearance... We look for and paint this inner, spiritual side of nature."', '"Nature,Today,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', '"Blue is the male principle, stern and spiritual. Yellow the female principle, gentle, cheerful and sensual. Red is matter, brutal and heavy and always the colour which must be fought and vanquished by the other two."', '"Blue,Spiritual,Gentle"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', '"Art is nothing but the expression of our dream; the more we surrender to it the closer we get to the inner truth of things, our dream-life, the true life that scorns questions and does not see them."', '"Life,Truth,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', '"Like everything genuine, its inner life guarantees its truth. All works of art created by truthful minds without regard for the work\'s conventional exterior remain genuine for all times."', '"Life,Work,Truth"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', 'Religions die slowly.', '"Die,Religions,Slowly"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', 'Serious art has been the work of individual artists whose art has had nothing to do with style because they were not in the least connected with the style or the needs of the masses. Their work arose rather in defiance of their times.', '"Work,Art,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', 'What appears spectral today will be natural tomorrow.', '"Today,Tomorrow,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe90', 'We are staunch and true and in rather a champagne mood.', '"Mood,True,Champagne"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Happy is the man who finds a true friend, and far happier is he who finds that true friend in his wife."', '"Marriage,Wife,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Nobody understands another\'s sorrow, and nobody another\'s joy."', '"Sad,Joy,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Every night when I go to bed, I hope that I may never wake again, and every morning renews my grief."', '"Hope,Morning,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"When I wished to sing of love, it turned to sorrow. And when I wished to sing of sorrow, it was transformed for me into love."', '"Love,Me,Sorrow"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"No one feels another\'s grief, no one understands another\'s joy. People imagine they can reach one another. In reality they only pass each other by."', '"Reality,Joy,People"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"You believe happiness to be derived from the place in which once you have been happy, but in truth it is centered in ourselves."', '"Happiness,Truth,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Easy mind, light heart. A mind that is too easy hides a heart that is too heavy."', '"Heart,Light,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'I try to decorate my imagination as much as I can.', '"Imagination,I Can,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'Why does God endow us with compassion?', '"God,Compassion,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'The greatest misfortune of the wise man and the greatest unhappiness of the fool are based upon convention.', '"Wise,Man,Wise Man"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"There are two contrary impulses which govern this man\'s brain-the one sane, and the other eccentric. They alternate at regular intervals."', '"Man,Two,Sane"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'The world resembles a stage on which every man is playing a part.', '"Man,World,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"There are eight girls in the house in which I am living, and practically all of them are good looking. You can realize that I am kept busy."', '"Good,Busy,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'A man endures misfortune without complaint.', '"Man,Misfortune,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'Approval or blame will follow in the world to come.', '"World,Blame,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"I am composing like a god, as if it simply had to be done as it has been done."', '"God,I Am,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'The manager is to be blamed who distributes parts to his players which they are unable to act.', '"Act,Players,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Why should the composer be more guilty than the poet who warms to fantasy by a strange flame, making an idea that inspires him the subject of his own very different treatment?"', '"Own,Fantasy,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', 'The moment is supreme.', '"Moment,Supreme"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"I never force myself to be devout except when I feel so inspired, and never compose hymns of prayers unless I feel within me real and true devotion."', '"Myself,Me,True"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"If only your pure and clean mind could touch me, dear Haydn, nobody has a greater reverence for you than I have."', '"Me,Mind,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"One bites into the brass mouthpiece of his wooden cudgel, and the other blows his cheeks out on a French horn. Do you call that Art?"', '"Art,Cheeks,Call"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Above all things, I must not get angry. If I do get angry I knock all the teeth out of the mouth of the poor wretch who has angered me."', '"Angry,Me,Poor"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe91', '"Our castle is not imposing, but is well built, and surrounded by a very fine garden. I live in the bailiff\'s house."', '"Castle,Live,Garden"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'There is a new hunger in the air for automotive design and looking to where automobiles are going in the future. Tesla will capture this through good design and engineering.', '"Future,Good,Design"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'Tesla is changing the paradigm. We\'re going to turn the world on its ear and create high demand through design.', '"Design,World,Create"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'The thing I love about electric vehicles is not stopping in gas stations. We\'re so accustomed to that... Now I\'m in control of when I refuel.', '"Love,Control,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'We seem to want one vehicle to carry people and soccer balls and hay bales.', '"People,Vehicle,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'Why shouldn\'t a car key look like a car?', '"Car,Look,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'Sports cars from the \'50s and \'60s are my favorites.', '"Sports,Favorites"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', '"My sister has kids, including two in baby seats, and she drives a minivan. I had to climb over the car seats to get into the back seat, and it seemed ridiculous to have to do gymnastics to get in and out of the car."', '"Car,Back,Climb"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', '"Model S has, really, the ready-to-wear elements. Gen 3 has the opportunity to be more couture."', '"Opportunity,More,Elements"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', '"Historically, there has been a gap between single-purpose racecars and street-legal models - commonly called supercars - that emulate the real racers on the road."', '"Road,Real,Gap"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'People want to feel good about the choices they make. They want to know they\'re choosing material that\'s not going to harm the environment.', '"Good,Feel Good,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'Why is it we want one car to do everything?', '"Car,Everything,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'I don\'t understand how I can pay $299 for iPhone and then get in my car and still have to turn knobs.', '"Car,I Can,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', '"We still see that people don\'t really realize that electric cars are here right now. And when we show up with an actual vehicle, and you see it drive away under its own power, it\'s still kind of a jaw-dropping moment for a lot of people."', '"Power,Moment,Drive"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'Women don\'t want an overly feminine vehicle - they want to feel secure.', '"Women,Feel,Vehicle"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'My mom marched into the reservation tent and reserved a Model X for herself. She drives a Jeep; she has four grandchildren. She didn\'t ask my dad. She just went ahead and did it.', '"Mom,Dad,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', '"We have an opportunity with the Model S to refine the design language, the surfacing, and all aspects of functionality."', '"Design,Opportunity,Language"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe94', 'We\'re looking for the early adopter who considers style to be an important part of the purchase decision. But they\'ll be getting a practical car with plenty of trunk space they can use for picking up building supplies at Home Depot.', '"Car,Space,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', 'Party domination and State leadership are concepts incompatible with one another.', '"Leadership,State,Domination"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', 'Names and individuals are unimportant when Germany\'s final fate is at stake.', '"Fate,Final,Germany"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', 'It is conceivable that a party might gain the majority in parliament and claims the government for itself.', '"Government,Parliament,Gain"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', 'It is to be hoped that the leaders of this movement will place the nation above the party.', '"Will,Place,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', '"We decline the claim to power by parties which want to own their followers body and soul, and which want to put themselves over and above the whole nation."', '"Power,Soul,Body"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', '"The nation demands a movement which has written upon its banner the internal and external national freedom that it will act as if it were the spiritual, social and political conscience of the nation."', '"Freedom,Political,Spiritual"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe95', 'The essence of conservative ideology is its being anchored in the divine order of things.', '"Conservative,Divine,Ideology"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe92', 'Religion is the everlasting dialogue between humanity and God. Art is its soliloquy.', '"God,Art,Religion"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe92', '"Yes, death is strong, but look you, the strongest, Stronger is music than death."', '"Death,Music,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"When I was nine, I started reading Homer. I would get up at four o\'clock in the morning, before I had to go to school, in third or fourth grade, and, for several hours, I would read \'The Iliad\' or \'The Odyssey.\'"', '"Morning,School,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'Beckett\'s \'Stories and Texts for Nothing\' is probably my favorite book.', '"Nothing,Book,Favorite"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'I write and have done so primarily for personal pleasure.', '"Done,Pleasure,Personal"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"When I\'m in certain moods, a conversation will start up in my head, and suddenly I\'ll realize that the language has reached a very high and interesting level, and then lines and stanzas will just kind of appear, full-blown."', '"Start,Will,Conversation"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"We know there are poets who are chosen: by what or whom, we no more know than what lies beyond our final breath, or what caused a certain action which resulted in the fulfillment or the desecration and collapse of what we most cared for in life."', '"Life,Action,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"I am in no way different from anyone else, that my predicament, my sense of aloneness or isolation may be precisely what unites me with everyone."', '"Me,I Am,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"For about twenty years, if I managed to write ten or twelve poems in a year; I considered that a pretty successful year, but I wrote \'The Beforelife\' within a year."', '"Year,Pretty,About"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'It\'s hard for me to grasp that I might somehow be my father\'s equal in any way.', '"Me,Father,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'Poetry endures when it possesses passionate and primally sincere clarity in the service of articulating universal human concerns.', '"Poetry,Service,Clarity"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"What I myself experience is indescribable gratitude in the face of God\'s perpetual and preemptive love, a love which is not contingent upon requital or even belief in His existence."', '"Love,God,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'I wish my father could be around.', '"Father,Wish,I Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'There are people who recall my father as a saint and a monster. I\'m quite sure I will share the same fate.', '"Father,People,Fate"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"Poetry, just because it is poetry, doesn\'t mean it is some kind of magic spell."', '"Poetry,Magic,Just Because"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"I\'ve always envied people who compose music or paint, because they don\'t have to be bothered with the sort of crude mess that language normally is, in everyday life and in the way we use it."', '"Life,Music,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', 'The poetic prose that most interests me is that of Henri Michaux.', '"Me,Most,Prose"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe93', '"I used to comfort myself with the idea of a book with serrated, detachable pages, so that you could read the thing the way it came and then shuffle the pages, like a giant deck of cards, and read the book in an entirely different order. It would be a different book, wouldn\'t it? It would be one of infinite books."', '"Myself,Way,Comfort"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9a', 'Good men died for our right to say whatever we want to say and use whatever words we want to use.', '"Good,Men,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9a', 'The truth is that Islam is not like any other faith. It is the religious equivalent of fascism.', '"Faith,Truth,Islam"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9a', '"People have their own opinions, they have the right to express them, they just don\'t have the right to attack you."', '"People,Own,Attack"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9a', '"You don\'t have to be Albert Einstein to see that we, as a race of people, we Australians, are being buried by a mass migration program to line the pockets of the rich and powerful."', '"Rich,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9a', 'I\'m not going to apologise or regret anything I say.', '"Regret,Anything,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9b', 'Never having children is a huge regret of mine.', '"Regret,Children,Having Children"', '2023-05-29 12:05:00', '2023-05-29 12:05:00'),
	('400350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9b', '"I would\'ve loved to have children and I\'m really good with kids, but I just didn\'t want to commit to anything when I had cancer. I didn\'t want to plan for the future."', '"Future,Good,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Versatility, quality, good passing... I think all that catches coaches\' eyes."', '"Good,Eyes,Quality"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I managed to do some classes in Ukraine but people there didn\'t really speak English. They spoke Russian so that\'s what I learned there.', '"People,Speak,Learned"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Neymar is a great player, it is so difficult to mark him."', '"Great,Difficult,Mark"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'The Ukrainian league isn\'t as strong as the Premier League.', '"Strong,Ukrainian,Premier League"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'You need to start games strongly and finish them strongly.', '"Start,Finish,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I\'m learning day by day.', '"Learning,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I have a big heart.', '"Heart,Big,Big Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"It\'s been a bit of a difficult start for me at United because I have not been playing so much. I had a lot of games in Shakhtar, but it\'s a little bit different here."', '"Me,Difficult,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"It\'s normal, of course, a process of adaptation to a different league."', '"Process,Normal,Course"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Ole has helped me a lot. He had a lot of chats with me.', '"Me,He,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I just want to continue doing what I\'m doing, playing well and starting the games - but I want to score, too."', '"Doing,Continue,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"All I ever wanted was to play regularly and now that I\'m doing that, there\'s no doubt my confidence is higher and that helps any player."', '"Confidence,Doubt,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Pogba is a great player.', '"Great,Player,Great Player"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'You will not build a team with 11 players.', '"Will,Build,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'You need a strong squad.', '"Squad,Strong,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"When everyone has the same goal, that\'s when we\'ll move forward."', '"Everyone,Same,Forward"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"That\'s what Brazilians are like - we\'re always having a laugh, we\'re always smiling, and my aim is to bring this spirit into the dressing room and onto the pitch, to play with a smile on my face."', '"Smile,Face,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Anderson is a really lively guy, a really cheerful guy."', '"Lively,Guy,Cheerful"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I was delighted to be called back into the Brazil squad. I think it was one of the most exciting moments of my life, just because of everything I had been through and it feeling like I had been given a second chance."', '"Life,Chance,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I have always been an extremely professional guy with everything.', '"Always,Professional,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I would never do anything that would harm me, and I am totally against using any kind of resource, illicitly, to benefit myself in any way."', '"Myself,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'We want to win the Europa League.', '"Win,Want,League"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"It\'s an honour to grab the attention of great coaches in Europe, from Manchester and from our own national team."', '"Great,Attention,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I think I am strong on the field, I am versatile, I can play in several midfield positions. Some coaches like that, it grabs their attention, it is a big deal for me."', '"Me,I Am,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'We have to shut up and work on the pitch.', '"Work,Shut Up,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Some critics are pointless - but many can offer me lessons.', '"Me,Critics,Offer"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I like to read what people are saying about my performances. With that, I can try to get better."', '"Better,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'England is the most competitive league in the world.', '"World,Competitive,England"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'A great coach like Guardiola and a great team like City... I would develop a lot with them.', '"Great,City,Great Team"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"It would be a dream to follow Fernandinho\'s footsteps, because he is my role model."', '"Role Model,Follow,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Everybody wants to be in the World Cup.', '"World,World Cup,Everybody"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I suffered a lot of criticism from the press and the fans, but I always kept motivating myself, working. I never dropped the shuttlecock."', '"Myself,Fans,Criticism"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I was even treated as a \'flop,\' a contract that doesn\'t pay. But I kept working my best."', '"Best,Contract,Pay"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"If people criticise, you have to keep working."', '"People,Keep,Working"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Sometimes it is good to hear criticism because you are more attentive.', '"Good,Sometimes,Criticism"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I think my ideal position is to join the attack a bit more like I did at Shakhtar. I played more as a box-to-box midfielder, so I played a little bit further forward."', '"Position,Attack,More"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Michael Carrick helps me a lot day-to-day. We always talk and he tries to help me with my positioning on the field. He\'s someone who always talks to me, which is important for adapting my football to the Premier League."', '"Football,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I want to be a big player and be part of the history of Man United. I already am, but I want to make history here at the club and to win some trophies, so that is my goal at Man United."', '"History,Man,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"The English league is difficult and has lots of big clubs but I think the derbies are the best games to play so, when we see the fixture list, we look at those games first."', '"Best,Look,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"It\'s hard to pick out a single team, because there are so many big games here in the Premier League, obviously there are the top teams like Liverpool, City, Chelsea, I think those big games, the \'big six\' are always good. We always look forward to them, we all want to be on the pitch and to win them."', '"Good,Look,City"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"We are all the same regardless of skin colour, hair and gender. We came from the same place and we all go to the same place when it\'s all said and done."', '"Skin,Hair,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'We need to treat all games equally and go after the wins because we need to keep improving.', '"Treat,Go,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I have already worked Dunga. He helped me at Internacional, making me a more defensive midfielder. But I can play as a first or second midfielder, like I do at Shakhtar."', '"Me,I Can,More"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I have changed a few things since playing in Europe, and for the better."', '"Better,Europe,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Foreign football is different and it has helped me evolve and mature, improving my attitude."', '"Attitude,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I know all young players have to work hard.', '"Work,Know,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"From my personal observations, the Spanish style of play, with a large number of passes, is somewhat similar to the Brazilian one."', '"Style,Personal,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Unfortunately, defeats are part of the game."', '"Game,Unfortunately,Part"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'It\'s very good for a 22-year-old player to feature in a Copa America.', '"Good,America,Feature"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"For me, I think the toughest player I came up against was Messi; he\'s out of this world, he\'s a genius. For me he\'s the best in the world, a great player and I think he\'s the toughest opponent I\'ve played against."', '"Best,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"When you play at a big club, there will always be competition - I\'m used to it. It\'s been like that from day one at United."', '"Competition,Day,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"For a club like Manchester United, it\'s not a good season without a title."', '"Good,Club,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"If we don\'t believe in ourselves, who else will?"', '"Believe,Will,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"My personal aim is to play a lot of games, put in great performances, do my best to help the team. Not get injured, obviously."', '"Best,Great,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Solskjaer is our teacher and does a good job.', '"Good,Teacher,Job"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I\'m very happy at Shakhtar.', '"Happy,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I have dreams of playing in major clubs in Europe.', '"Dreams,Europe,Playing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'It\'s an honour to be on the radar of great European coaches.', '"Great,Radar,Honour"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Guardiola is a great manager, but I chose to join another great manager, Mourinho, at United."', '"Great,Join,United"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'My father signed me up for football training when I was only four and my grandfather also used to take me.', '"Football,Me,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'When I was 10 I started playing for Atletico Mineiro and that was the start of my professional career.', '"Start,Professional,Playing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'My family have always supported me to develop my football.', '"Family,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I played for Atletico and Internacional and then moved to Ukraine with Shakhtar Donetsk. My family supported me a lot and I\'m very thankful for them.', '"Family,Thankful,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"For me, Manchester United means greatness."', '"Me,Greatness,Manchester United"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"To work with Jose Mourinho, who has won so many trophies in his time as a coach, is an opportunity not to be missed."', '"Work,Time,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I\'m really happy to be working with Jose Mourinho. He\'s a great person and he\'s always keen to communicate with the squad and help people to be communicative regarding what they\'re to do on the pitch.', '"Great,People,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'We are all friends here at United. But it is good to feel that everyone wants a spot in the starting XI.', '"Good,Feel,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I am the kind of guy who you\'ll always see smiling. My childhood was like this. I had a lot of fun. We had a bad environment, but we also learned how to cope with it."', '"Childhood,I Am,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Because I was called a flop ever since I got here, my only intention is to be part of Manchester United\'s history."', '"History,Intention,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"When people hear a footballer speaking, they can think about it and maybe even reconsider the prejudices they have."', '"People,Footballer,Hear"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"When the fixture list is released, while you\'re on holiday, wherever it is in the world, it reminds you and it makes you hungry to play again."', '"World,Hungry,Holiday"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"In the Premier League it is difficult, the midfield is very congested; there is a lot of pressure and the game is very fast. So it\'s hard for you to spend a lot of time with the ball; you have to be very fast, you have to think long before the ball reaches you."', '"Time,Game,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I don\'t say that there is a lot of difference between Fred from Shakhtar and Manchester, we are adapting. Here at United, I score a little more, I improved a lot. I think that is the main difference."', '"Difference,More,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I always watched a lot of English football. It has always been really strong.', '"Football,Always,English Football"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I used to watch United, Manchester City, Chelsea and Arsenal, when Gilberto Silva used to play there."', '"City,Chelsea,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'My wife talks a lot with Fernandinho and Ederson\'s wives.', '"Wife,Wives,Lot"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Fonseca allows me to play both offensively and defensively, and my main task is to change the direction of attacking moves."', '"Change,Me,Direction"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I know that I have to run all the game and don\'t stop or I will be useless to the team.', '"Game,Useless,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I like Manchester. My family are here and they like it too.', '"Family,Here,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Personally, I\'m happy how I played in my first \'clasico\' against Liverpool."', '"Happy,First,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Passing is one of my main objectives in the game and when I make a lot of passes I\'m happy.', '"Game,Happy,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Obviously I\'m not happy when I miss the passes so I look to get that right. I work very hard on that.', '"Work,Look,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I know my job is not to score goals, but when I\'m scoring goals I\'m very happy."', '"Goals,Know,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I don\'t think anyone likes to draw very much, we will always go in to win."', '"Win,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"My body is my work tool, right?"', '"Work,Body,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I\'m very grateful to all my family, especially my mum of course."', '"Family,Grateful,Course"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"My mum left her job to allow me to pursue my dreams, coming along with me. But the person who really inspired me was my grandfather. He\'ll always have a very special place in my heart."', '"Dreams,Heart,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'We can\'t choose who we play against.', '"Choose,Play,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'There are many Brazilians standing out in the Premier League.', '"Standing,Premier League,Out"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I really like Kante, I admire him, he\'s a guy who plays great football."', '"Great,Football,Admire"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'Son is another guy that I admire a lot.', '"Son,Admire,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'When I got to Ukraine the league was strong.', '"Strong,Ukraine,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Gilberto was a top midfielder who played for Arsenal. But he has a lot of respect for Manchester United, who are obviously a big club here in England. He praised the club a lot and, after he was granted the opportunity to speak to Jose Mourinho and other senior figures at United, we made the decision together for me to come here."', '"Respect,Opportunity,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Gilberto is a top guy and his advice means a lot to me. He played in the same position as I do and he won the Premier League, so I look to him for inspiration, I listen to what he has to say and I take on board what he tells me."', '"Look,Me,Advice"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I\'m really happy to have got married and, thanks to Manchester United, I was able to get my whole family together with my wife on the day."', '"Family,Together,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'I feel really grateful to the Man United fans and whenever I\'m on the pitch I\'ll aim to do my best for all the fans to get the win and make them happy.', '"Best,Man,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', 'It\'s a huge club with great history and it\'s a real honour to perform for United.', '"History,Great,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"Manchester United is a huge club. When I was young, it was a name I used to hear and it was a name I used to see on computer games and I used to play with the team."', '"See,Name,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9c', '"I\'m looking to show the best of my abilities every day and to work to improve, and that means working to play well and put in good performances in the Premier League and with Manchester United to achieve great things and win titles."', '"Work,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'I\'d rather have a full bottle in front of me than a full frontal lobotomy.', '"Me,Rather,Bottle"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"A celebrity is a person who works hard all of their life to become well known, and then wears dark glasses to avoid being recognized."', '"Life,Famous,Glasses"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"I like long walks, especially when they are taken by people who annoy me."', '"Funny,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"A committee is a group of people who individually can do nothing, but who, as a group, can meet and decide that nothing can be done."', '"People,Nothing,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"I learned law so well, the day I graduated I sued the college, won the case, and got my tuition back."', '"Graduation,Day,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"A committee is a group of the unprepared, appointed by the unwilling to do the unnecessary."', '"Group,Committee,Unnecessary"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'California is a fine place to live - if you happen to be an orange.', '"Funny,Live,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"You can take all the sincerity in Hollywood, place it in the navel of a fruit fly and still have room enough for three caraway seeds and a producer\'s heart."', '"Fruit,Heart,Fly"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"I play a musical instrument a little, but only for my own amazement."', '"Amazing,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Most of us spend the first six days of each week sowing wild oats; then we go to church on Sunday and pray for a crop failure.', '"Failure,Wild,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"A conference is a gathering of people who singly can do nothing, but together can decide that nothing can be done."', '"Together,People,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Hanging is too good for a man who makes puns; he should be drawn and quoted.', '"Good,Man,Hanging"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"My father never raised his hand to any one of his children, except in self-defense."', '"Dad,Father,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'California is a great place to live if you\'re an orange.', '"Great,Live,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
