	('400469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'The last time I saw him he was walking down lover\'s lane holding his own hand.', '"Funny,Time,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'I can\'t understand why a person will take a year to write a novel when he can easily buy one for a few dollars.', '"Will,Person,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Committee - a group of men who individually can do nothing but as a group decide that nothing can be done.', '"Men,Nothing,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
