	('400473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Television is the triumph of machine over people.', '"People,Television,Triumph"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"Life, in my estimation, is a biological misadventure that we terminate on the shoulders of six strange men whose only objective is to make a hole in one with you."', '"Life,Men,Strange"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"I always have trouble remembering three things: faces, names, and - I can\'t remember what the third thing is."', '"Remember,Three,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'I have just returned from Boston. It is the only thing to do if you find yourself up there.', '"Travel,Yourself,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"A telescope will magnify a star a thousand times, but a good press agent can do even better."', '"Good,Better,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Some movie stars wear their sunglasses even in church. They\'re afraid God might recognize them and ask for autographs.', '"God,Fear,Stars"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"It is probably not love that makes the world go around, but rather those mutually supportive alliances through which partners recognize their dependence on each other for the achievement of shared and private goals."', '"Love,World,Achievement"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'An actor\'s popularity is fleeting. His success has the life expectancy of a small boy who is about to look into a gas tank with a lighted match.', '"Life,Success,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"If I could get my membership fee back, I\'d resign from the human race."', '"Back,Race,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Washington is no place for a good actor. The competition from bad actors is too great.', '"Good,Great,Competition"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Television is a device that permits people who haven\'t anything to do to watch people who can\'t do anything.', '"People,Television,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'The vice-president of an advertising agency is a bit of executive fungus that forms on a desk that has been exposed to conference.', '"Advertising,Desk,Conference"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"We are living in the machine age. For the first time in history the comedian has been compelled to supply himself with jokes and comedy material to compete with the machine. Whether he knows it or not, the comedian is on a treadmill to oblivion."', '"History,Time,Age"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'An income tax form is like a laundry list - either way you lose your shirt.', '"Lose,Shirt,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'The first thing that strikes a visitor to Paris is a taxi.', '"First,Taxi,Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Ed Sullivan will be around as long as someone else has talent.', '"Long,Talent,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'All I know about humor is that I don\'t know anything about it.', '"Humor,Know,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"Treat employees like partners, and they act like partners."', '"Treat,Act,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Radio is a bag of mediocrity where little men with carbon minds wallow in sluice of their own making.', '"Men,Bag,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'During the Samuel Johnson days they had big men enjoying small talk; today we have small men enjoying big talk.', '"Men,Today,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', '"What\'s on your mind, if you will allow the overstatement."', '"Mind,Will,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'A gentleman is any man who wouldn\'t hit a woman with his hat on.', '"Man,Hat,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'An associate producer is the only guy in Hollywood who will associate with a producer.', '"Will,Hollywood,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'My uncle is a Southern planter. He\'s an undertaker in Alabama.', '"Uncle,He,Alabama"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'The advertising world had space men in it before spacemen existed.', '"Space,Men,World"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'I don\'t want to own anything that won\'t fit into my coffin.', '"Own,Anything,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9e', 'Her hat is a creation that will never go out of style; it will just look ridiculous year after year.', '"Look,Style,Hat"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Fereydun, that\'s my dad\'s name. My grandmother, my dad\'s mom, when she was pregnant, she was dating a man from Persia, a Persian gentleman. It wasn\'t his child, but he was still very supportive and said, \'Hey, this is a great name,\' and so it stuck. So that\'s what she named him."', '"Great,Dating,Mom"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Everyone knows deep in their hearts that the drums are the coolest instrument, and that a band is only as good as its drummer. So I\'m all for drum solos. I\'m all for drummers hamming it up. I\'m all for drummers standing up and kicking over the kit."', '"Good,Drummer,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"My mom is from Venezuela, and my dad is German and Japanese, and we lived in Brazil when I was a kid for a couple of years, and then I grew up on Long Island. I think all the traveling and all the nationalities put that stuff in my head. I was just around it a lot."', '"Mom,Dad,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"My father came from Germany. My mom came from Venezuela. My father\'s culturally German, but his father was Japanese. I was raised in New York and spent two years in Rio. My parents met at the University of Southern Mississippi, and they had me there, and then we moved to New York. I\'m not very familiar with Mississippi."', '"Mom,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Every day, I wanna work on being a better person, not just to others but to myself."', '"Work,Myself,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Wayne Coyne has put out Flaming Lips records in gummy bear skulls and all these different kinds of packaging that\'s really, really inventive. And that\'s what you should always do."', '"Always,Lips,Bear"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Surround yourself with people you like and respect; surround yourself with people you just want to be around and keep making things.', '"Respect,Surround Yourself,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I have a problem with sweets. I have an inability to eat a just little bit. It\'s almost like I can\'t even enjoy chocolate anymore - I have to stuff it into my brain, cram it into my ears."', '"Brain,Sweets,Chocolate"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"All of my memories are now on hard drives. I\'ll change phones or I\'ll change my laptop, and all my photos stay."', '"Change,Memories,Laptop"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Hopefully there will be a day when all comedy is all robots.', '"Day,Will,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When I used to see Rick Moranis do something, to me that was immediately funny. Or George Carlin or Martin Lawrence."', '"Funny,Me,See"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'No yoga. I can barely sit down.', '"I Can,Down,Sit"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When you\'re being mean to someone, you can feel the audience just get cold."', '"Feel,Someone,Mean"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"People on the street comment on how handsome I am. You know, people stop and say how angular my face is."', '"Face,Handsome,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'My favorite song is \'Cybele\'s Reverie\' by Stereolab.', '"Song,Favorite,Reverie"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"If something seems like a little venue, don\'t treat it like that. Do it all. If you\'re sort of wondering why you\'re doing something at some location, just do it - any size theater, production, or whatever. It\'s all helpful."', '"Treat,Doing,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Sometimes in Portland I\'m like, \'Who is funding this city?\' It\'s doing great - there\'s all these new shops; there\'s a synthesizer store. Where is this coming from?"', '"Great,City,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I\'m drawn to punk. I\'m drawn to samba a bit. I don\'t think there\'s a type of music I\'m not drawn to. Lykke Li I really like. Holy Sons I still can\'t get enough of.', '"Music,Enough,Punk"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"The Long Island experience is so strange. You\'re a satellite around the city, so the presence of the city is always looming."', '"Experience,Long,City"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"As far as value goes, obviously it\'s nicer to be in an environment where you feel comfortable. But it\'s also clear that it\'s probably not the most realistic thing."', '"Value,Feel,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"For me, I would get so frustrated because I would see these other bands just whip by us."', '"Me,See,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I enjoy getting to work on \'Saturday Night Live\', where I get to do people like David Paterson. And then, its like a different muscle to do someone like a bicycle guy on\' Portlandia\'."', '"Work,Night,Bicycle"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When punk came along, it made perfect sense to me. I found it melodic. The Clash, Buzzcocks."', '"Me,Perfect,Punk"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I\'m so glad cities have personalities, just like people have personalities. That\'s something that makes me smile."', '"Smile,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Discomfort is the way to go if you want to make something you feel is worthwhile.', '"Way,Feel,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I love my bandmates, and they\'re my friends, and even though we had fun and got to tour and I got to play the drums a lot, which I\'ll always appreciate, we had a really rough time. We toured and tried to get people to come to our shows and put out records, and we really struggled."', '"Love,Time,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I would see people on TV, or I\'d see bands I really liked, and I thought, \'I want that.\'"', '"People,See,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I\'ve met Tony Danza. He was really nice. And he looks... I feel like he hasn\'t aged. He looks exactly the same. He\'s just Tony Danza. He\'s exactly the same as he\'s always been.', '"Feel,Always,Nice"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I have an inability to relax. I try to make every day a work day. I get pleasure from work... I try to think of sketch ideas, stand-up pieces. I am incapable of leisure and leisure time."', '"Work,Time,Relax"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"For some reason, juggling things makes everything work better. That\'s just how we operate. It just makes the other project more of something to look forward to. I think the more you keep things going, the more it helps the other project."', '"Work,Look,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"El Perro del Mar sort of accompanied my time at \'SNL.\' To concentrate and focus, I would play the bass to one of her songs from her third album."', '"Time,Focus,My Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Even when I go do comedy stuff live, I can still feel the drummer in me about to go onstage."', '"Me,Feel,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I can\'t relax. I\'m not happy unless I\'m working on stuff. \'SNL\' is always a huge workload, as enjoyable as it is."', '"Relax,Happy,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I will always, no matter what, be a punk more than anything."', '"Will,Always,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I\'ve always been a fan of instructional videos. The bass-player ones are insane. The music on them is fascinating. It\'s not something you hear on CDs or would really ever play in bands. You listen to it and are like, \'What is happening?\' It\'s this blizzard of notes in weird time signatures, and they\'re trying to teach you that."', '"Time,Music,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I feel really lucky to get to do comedy, and music, at all. I want to do as much as I can."', '"Music,Feel,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I think a comedian has a more specific job. Whereas a musician can fall into different categories, you know, of making background music or doing a soundtrack or wanting to be in a band or writing the song, or writing your own songs. And then comedy is a very black and white thing. You want to make people happy."', '"Music,Black And White,Black"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Sometimes \'Portlandia\' can be pretty traditional. But the stuff I\'ve always loved on \'SNL\' has always been the weirdest stuff I\'ve done. The stuff that went on at 10 to 1 in the morning.', '"Morning,Sometimes,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I feel bad for everyone I\'ve gone out with.', '"Bad,Feel,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I came away from \'Saturday Night Live\' feeling very well represented. I felt, and I still feel like, they let me do so much stuff that I wanted to do. Stuff that I almost didn\'t even know what it was."', '"Night,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I think I was a terrible husband, I think I\'m a terrible boyfriend."', '"Husband,Terrible,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I want it all... fast. I want to be married, I want to live together... and then somewhere around a year or two years, I get freaked out. I freak out emotionally and then I actually feel like \'Oh my God, who\'s this stranger in my house?\'"', '"God,Together,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I love \'Saturday Night Live,\' and I really feel like people who have left before me have always stayed with the show. They never really quite left, which is nice. Everyone kind of stays close."', '"Love,Night,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I spent a lot of time lifting my drums into a van, playing to ten people night after night. I can\'t complain about anything now. That stuff was heavy."', '"Time,Night,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Steve Jobs was a real rock star to me. I looked forward to his products like people look forward to albums.', '"Look,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"The day of parts of the country hating each other, or rivalries like that... I feel like that\'s dead."', '"Day,Dead,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Bill Hader does a really good impression of me.', '"Good,Me,Impression"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"There\'s something really easy and just somehow un-crowded about the Portland airport. Every time I go there I\'m like, \'Why is this so easy and sweet?\'"', '"Time,Sweet,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"At \'SNL\' there\'s framed pictures of all the cast members, and it starts with Dan Aykroyd. It\'s linear. It just keeps going through all these people, and then you\'re at the end of it."', '"People,End,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When I first started going to Portland, people told me about Stumptown. They were like \'Oh, it\'s the best coffee,\' and I thought, \'How good could it really be?\' I\'m like, \'Sure, great, uh... I\'d love to see it.\' But then when I went, it truly, I am not kidding, is the best coffee I have ever had."', '"Love,Best,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Chalkboards being used inside the restaurant seem to be a good sign that the proprietors are proud of their food, and that\'s kind of nice, actually - it\'s a nice personal touch."', '"Good,Food,Restaurant"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Prince is my favorite ever. I\'ve liked Prince since... It\'s been a really long time. Even in junior high. I used to only like punk for a while, and I had all these rules for what kinds of groups were cool, and who was not cool, but as soon as I saw this one Prince video... It just broke all those rules. I was like, \'I love this no matter what.\'"', '"Love,Cool,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When people say that L.A. doesn\'t have a culture, I think it really does: a very old culture, and very specific. There\'s streets named after entertainers, and statues of entertainers, and it\'s great. Entertainment is still art, even if it makes billions of dollars. So it\'s like a city built on entertainment, and art in a way."', '"Art,Great,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I would really like to do a movie. Schedule-wise I don\'t know when exactly, but I think it would be great to do a Portlandia movie. Some of my favorite television shows have done it and they\'ve been great. Like Monty Python. I think it would be great."', '"Great,Done,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I loooved Sleater-Kinney like a crazy person.', '"Crazy,Person,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I try to maintain a high level of coolness. Which means I\'ve gotta look at lot of magazines. I\'ve gotta look at a lot of ads to see what people want to wear.', '"Look,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I don\'t think there\'s an archetype for the Justin Bieber fan. A Bieber fan just looks like an American. You wouldn\'t even need a costume to try and resemble one.', '"American,Try,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Every music journalist I\'ve ever met has been stunningly beautiful.', '"Music,Beautiful,Every"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"There are bands that I am friends with, who will invite me up on stage. Like Les Savy Fav, who have had me on stage, and I have played on their record. There are a couple of bands like that. Yo La Tengo has invited me to play with them."', '"Me,I Am,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"There are people who are genetically made to start record labels, and I\'m not one of those people. People just have it in their blood and are good at it. Corey Rusk from Touch and Go and Ian MacKaye. These are people who have made their own labels."', '"Good,People,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I tend to think that there is a sophistication to everything at \'Saturday Night Live,\' including the sketches."', '"Night,Live,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I\'m obsessed with my 20s. I buy things that I wanted in my 20s. It\'s weird; it\'s a weird thing that I didn\'t grow out of.', '"Grow,Weird,Buy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I am opposed to vacations and leisure. I try to make every day a work day. Even if there\'s nothing on my schedule, I will try do at least one task that is work-related."', '"Work,I Am,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I am immediately disinterested when I hear mountain-climbing stories.', '"I Am,Hear,Am"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'My favorite album is \'Ram\' by Paul and Linda McCartney.', '"Album,Ram,Favorite"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I\'m glad I get to do characters. It\'s just like a Polaroid shot of whoever the person is, and to me, anyway, that\'s kind of what life is like. You get a general sense of somebody, and then we\'re all good, we get it. We understand each other."', '"Life,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I wanted so badly to be in a famous band, and it was not happening. I played drums with different bands and with the Blue Man Group in Chicago, but I definitely felt like, \'Wow, I did not picture my life being like this.\'"', '"Life,Famous,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When you\'re in a band, you spend most of your time in a van. Like, there were four of us, we toured all the time, and you\'re stuck looking at three other people for a month straight. And all of those times, we all just liked making fun of people, doing impressions of people, coming up with songs."', '"Time,Fun,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I can\'t be bothered with narrative. It takes too long for me to try to think of it.', '"Me,Long,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I travel a lot. I\'ll go back and forth, you know, West Coast-East Coast, but it\'s separated by segments. So it\'s not a daily thing."', '"Travel,Daily,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I actually, legitimately feel that I\'m not busy enough. I want to be so busy that it\'s overwhelming."', '"Busy,Feel,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"That\'s one of the great things about Los Angeles, that people just play music, and it\'s all very welcoming and welcomed."', '"Music,Great,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Panned or not, \'Dune\' is a real part of science-fiction filmmaking."', '"Filmmaking,Real,Part"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I don\'t know anything about the wine world at all.', '"World,Know,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I love painters because I don\'t paint, so I get to enjoy art; I like collecting paintings."', '"Love,Art,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I spent most of my 20s playing music. I was in a band, and we worked really hard and did not get very far."', '"Music,Hard,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I was really close to being this guy who used to be in this band who is still playing and trying to get some recordings together, but I got really lucky."', '"Together,Trying,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'There\'s no judgment on bands that continue on who aren\'t popular; some people get enjoyment out of it. I\'m just not one of those people.', '"People,Continue,Some People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I feel like Miami is way, way too hot."', '"Hot,Way,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I love driving. Listen to some music.', '"Love,Music,Driving"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I find it weird to use my own voice on TV.', '"Weird,Voice,My Own"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I think Ian MacKaye is everything that I always wanted to be.', '"Always,Everything,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Over the years, El Perro del Mar became this artist that, every record that came out, I just loved it."', '"Loved,Artist,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When \'Pale Fire\' came out, that album was a big friend of mine. I\'ve just always purely been a fan of El Perro del Mar."', '"Fire,Big,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I\'d want to direct a video for Yoko Ono. As long as I got to work with Yoko Ono someday, I\'d be really happy. I just think she\'s such a great artist - it would just be so nice."', '"Work,Great,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I would never play a character that wasn\'t true. It\'s not a moral thing; it\'s just that it\'s more convincing if it\'s a little bit like me.', '"Character,Me,True"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I\'m not by nature a cynical person. But sometimes your expectations are different from reality.', '"Nature,Reality,Expectations"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I was actually late to the punk movement because I was too young.', '"Late,Young,Punk"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"The bands that were big in \'77, like the Clash and the Sex Pistols and Talking Heads, I got into them in the early \'80s. And it changed my life. It got into my DNA."', '"Life,Sex,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I will always consider myself a punk because of those experiences in high school. It will always be a part of me.', '"Myself,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Missing something doesn\'t help anything. You can only look at the future, what you can keep doing."', '"Future,Look,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"The way James Franco goes to new projects, he does it the way an artist should, which is with a question mark. Like, will this work?"', '"Work,Way,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"You should approach everything in life like, \'What is this?\'"', '"Life,Everything,Approach"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'There\'s almost no such thing as a hipster.', '"Almost,Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I was impersonating people way, way, way early, as far back as I can remember. And I would do people on my street for my parents, I remember. And in school, I did the same thing with all the teachers. It was just like, I mean, it was something I loved to do. I don\'t think there was a time when I wasn\'t doing it. I was always doing it."', '"Time,Parents,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I really loved touring with my band, but it felt like we would spend a lot of time playing in empty rooms - empty clubs. We had some good successes, but it\'s so physically hard to load up a van and drive all day."', '"Time,Good,Drive"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I really like watching TV at home.', '"Home,Watching,Watching Tv"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I believe in limitations. I think the worst art ever made - in my opinion, because it\'s all so subjective - is where the artist had complete freedom."', '"Freedom,Art,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I\'ll just say that there are times when TV shows, like \'The Honeymooners\' or \'I Love Lucy\' or something, where they\'re totally in their stride, and this thing happens, where you can tell they got everything they wanted. And it starts to look a little relaxed. No criticism to the shows whatsoever; these people are geniuses."', '"Love,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I take any project on a month or two at a time. Meaning, I don\'t think too far ahead."', '"Time,Ahead,Project"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'We almost called the \'Portlandia\' show \'Stumptown.\' That was the original name.', '"Name,Show,Almost"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Everywhere I go, somebody says something to me. It\'s really nice."', '"Me,Go,Nice"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Art should not be an easy thing.', '"Art,Easy,Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'The worst art is when it\'s really convenient and comfy.', '"Art,Worst,Convenient"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"My showbiz career started with \'SNL,\' and to write an \'SNL\' book... well, there are already enough of those."', '"Enough,Well,Book"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I get very, very little sleep."', '"Sleep,Get,Little"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'My problem is with intimacy. That\'s where I have my biggest problems.', '"Problems,Problem,Where"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I have the capability to have a close relationship with someone.', '"Relationship,Someone,Close"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Something about Portland just really resonated with me.', '"Me,Something,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I like that \'Broad City\' exists, and I love being around at the same time as \'Key & Peele.\' I love those guys - I just, I love their faces."', '"Love,Time,City"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"One person who was interesting was Jello Biafra, who was - of all things - very professional!"', '"Person,Professional,Interesting"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"As a kid, \'The Monkees\' was such a cool show. I had such a thrill saying, \'OMG, I was in a sketch with one of the Monkees.\'"', '"Cool,Saying,Show"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Ever since I was really little, I started doing a - I don\'t know how to put this - mentally challenged person on my street. I meant no harm by it, but I remembered how this person talked, and I did it for my mom, and she was not into it. She said, \'You can\'t do that!\' But my dad really laughed."', '"Mom,Dad,Street"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I really like Au Revoir Simone.', '"Like,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'There should be comedians who perform only for robots - I\'m saying human comedians that only perform for robots.', '"Robots,Human,Saying"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I can only parody stuff I love.', '"Love,I Can,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'Music documentaries are tricky because of \'Spinal Tap.\' That movie has stood the test of time.', '"Time,Music,Tricky"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Talking Heads were a big influence on my comedy. For David Byrne, every album had to be different. With \'Portlandia,\' every season has to be different. You gotta reinvent the look, all of it."', '"Look,Influence,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Before \'SNL,\' I would do stand-up, opening for Jeff Tweedy. It was worse than bombing in that people were dead silent."', '"Dead,People,Opening"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I don\'t think I\'ve ever hosted anything in my life.', '"Life,My Life,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"When I\'m hungry, I need to eat right away."', '"Hungry,Right,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Since I was, like, an infant... I remember being in love with television. I loved listening to music. I wanted to be on records, and I wanted to be on TV."', '"Love,Music,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I see everything as a positive that can only help me.', '"Positive,Me,See"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I learned at \'SNL\' that it\'s a bummer to bum people out.', '"People,Learned,Bum"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'You have to understand how lucky I feel. I was on \'Saturday. Night. Live.\' I played with the Clash! On what planet would I look at anything in my life in any less-than-stellar way?', '"Life,Night,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', 'I work better when I\'m juggling projects. Nothing worse than watching someone really embrace what they\'re doing if they love it too much.', '"Love,Work,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I will admit that I purposely stress myself out. But I think I like stressing myself out. There\'s a glamour to, like, \'I\'ve got to get to the airport!\' I just like the caricature."', '"Myself,Stress,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I don\'t like watching shows where all of a sudden you\'re like, what happened? They shot the last season in Las Vegas?"', '"Watching,Shot,Last"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I started comedy in, like, 1998."', '"Comedy,Like,Started"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '\'Sandinista!\' is a masterpiece.', 'Masterpiece', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"James Franco has turned his life into a real art project. In my opinion, that\'s the way to live."', '"Life,Art,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"Questlove redefined what a band can be, and Paul Shaffer and Max Weinberg really put their own spin on it. I bow down to these people. All of them."', '"People,Own,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fe9f', '"I like to think Portland and L.A. are not rivals; they\'re cousins. As cities on the West Coast, they\'re distinct in their own way but still culturally similar."', '"Way,Own,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'The hardest job kids face today is learning good manners without seeing any.', '"Good,Learning,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', '"This search for what you want is like tracking something that doesn\'t want to be tracked. It takes time to get a dance right, to create something memorable."', '"Time,Search,Dance"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', '"The higher up you go, the more mistakes you are allowed. Right at the top, if you make enough of them, it\'s considered to be your style."', '"Style,Mistakes,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'I have no desire to prove anything by dancing. I have never used it as an outlet or a means of expressing myself. I just dance. I just put my feet in the air and move them around.', '"Myself,Feet,Dance"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'I just put my feet in the air and move them around.', '"Feet,Air,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'Dancing is a sweat job.', '"Sweat,Job,Dancing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'Disco is just jitterbug.', '"Disco,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea0', 'I don\'t want to be the oldest performer in captivity... I don\'t want to look like a little old man dancing out there.', '"Man,Look,Old Man"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', '"Obama sounded like Al Gore on global warming. The more the case for man-made warming falls apart, the more hysterical Gore gets about an imminent catastrophe. The more public support his stimulus bill loses, the more Obama embraces fear-mongering."', '"Support,Global Warming,More"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', '"Obama specializes in knocking down straw men. \'I reject the view that says our problems will simply take care of themselves,\' he said, implying that\'s the view of Republicans. It\'s the view of almost no one."', '"Men,View,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', '"The mainstream media may have trouble resisting the temptation to declare that Karl Rove has been demoted, but the truth is quite the contrary. By giving up his role as deputy White House chief of staff, Rove has been freed to do what he does best: shape big issues and develop strategies to win elections."', '"Best,Truth,Media"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', 'President Obama insists he\'s a free-market guy. But you have to wonder whether he understands how a free economy really works.', '"Free,Wonder,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', 'Candidates don\'t have to deal with reality. They talk about the wonderful things they can accomplish as if advocating them is the same as achieving them. They live in a world of political make-believe in which everything from reconciling conflicting interests to paying for costly programs is easy.', '"Political,Reality,World"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea1', '"Presidents with strong nerves are decisive. They don\'t balk at unpopular decisions. They are willing to make people angry. Bush had strong nerves. Clinton, who passed up a chance to eliminate Osama bin Laden, did not. Obama is a people pleaser, a trait not normally associated with nerves of steel."', '"Chance,Angry,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'How does a project get to be a year late? One day at a time.', '"Time,Day,One Day At A Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'Good judgment comes from experience and experience comes from bad judgment.', '"Experience,Good,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'How does a project get to be a year behind schedule? One day at a time.', '"Time,Day,One Day At A Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', '"There is no single development, in either technology or management technique, which by itself promises even one order-of-magnitude improvement within a decade in productivity, in reliability, in simplicity."', '"Technology,Improvement,Simplicity"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'Adding manpower to a late software project makes it later.', '"Late,Project,Software"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'The fundamental problem with program maintenance is that fixing a defect has a substantial chance of introducing another.', '"Chance,Maintenance,Problem"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea2', 'Systematically identity top designers as early as possible. The best are often not the most experienced.', '"Best,Identity,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I will say I love competing, and I was in a great era of playing with young Phil Mickelson and older Greg Norman and Nick Price. I don\'t know if YA Title could throw the ball these days, but you can play golf for a long, long time."', '"Love,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I caddied for a guy who was a very good player, and he gave me a set of clubs, just a starter set: 5-iron, 7-iron, 9-iron, putter and driver. I just loved it. How I developed my swing was to just grab a club and start banging balls."', '"Good,Me,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"My mom was so people-friendly. She was incredible. She\'d go to the mall, and she\'d talk to everyone. Give people a kiss on the cheek. I think if I wasn\'t pushed around a lot, I\'d be great with people. Maybe I still can be."', '"Great,Mom,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I used to break a lot of clubs. I probably was a little different than your average junior player. I did have a lot longer hair and a lot more brown hair. But my demeanor, you know, really from maybe my second, third year on Tour, has gotten a lot more even keel."', '"Hair,Know,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', 'I\'m not very good in the rain. I don\'t wear a golf glove.', '"Good,Rain,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I\'m a lot older than I was when I was 30, which is kind of hard to believe."', '"Believe,Hard,Older"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I can say I won a Senior British Open at Turnberry. I think that\'s the best thing about it, the whole week, was playing this course. It\'s a challenging, very tough course, under extreme weather. But you know, it\'s nice to win any event."', '"Best,Weather,Tough"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I could go away five or six weeks in a row and never touch a club. I would just look at them and say, \'I just don\'t want to; it\'s not that important.\' And it wasn\'t that important. Golf - I don\'t want to answer loosely - I pay a lot of attention to it, but I don\'t ever really think about it."', '"Look,Important,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"Golf is a game to me. Other players work extremely hard all year long. I work hard before Augusta. I know I get good results when I practice, but it also wears me out. It literally wore me out even when I was in my 20s."', '"Work,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"My goal has always been to play golf, and play it well. In the end, that\'s what I am, a golfer. If my back lets me, I\'m going to play my favorite places. If I hurt myself, that\'ll probably be it for a while."', '"Myself,Me,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I think people like players they can relate to. It seems as if people think they know me. I just think I\'m an ordinary Joe who plays golf very, very well."', '"Me,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"Golf is supposed to be fun, but I don\'t think anything is fun if you\'re not doing it reasonably well."', '"Fun,Doing,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I left home at 17, traveled. I got married when I was 21. That\'s a young age. As it turned out, things were fine, then not so fine, and then it was a blunder. That happens all the time."', '"Time,Age,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"Really in all my years on Tour, in the U.S. Open I probably played great golf in two of them, out of maybe 20, so it\'s a lot of work."', '"Work,Great,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea3', '"I\'m pretty much a self-taught player. My swing hasn\'t changed a whole lot, I don\'t think. But I watch a lot of people."', '"People,Swing,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea4', '"Whenever I design any variant, or when anybody sends me one, I always say if at all possible within the context of the game don\'t have two home supply centers touching each other."', '"Home,Design,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea4', '"I think most people played both variants and regular games. It was a period when variants were very popular and there were a lot more variants being played at that time. Every week practically, it seemed someone would publish a new variant in a zine."', '"Time,New,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea4', '"Then, all of a sudden, he stopped and nobody heard from him or got a response to orders. At this point Rod Walker looked him up and found he was living in a commune and seemed to be dropping out of the hobby."', '"Nobody,Living,Hobby"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'Profit or perish... There are only two ways to make money: increase sales and decrease costs.', '"Money,Two,Profit"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"From my point of view, what I really like, what I think is really terrific about my work, is that the company\'s had the opportunity to train literally thousands and thousands of brand new franchisees to successfully run their very first business."', '"Work,Business,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"If someone wants to eat healthy, they can do that and get the sandwich exactly right. I\'m so pleased we\'re able to influence so many people and their eating habits."', '"Influence,People,Eating"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"If I\'m spending time on something, I may as well do good as opposed to average."', '"Time,Good,Spending Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"There may be a perception that, with franchises, they\'re all the same, so that limits the ability to experiment. But that\'s not true. We\'ve always kept two slots open on the menu of each Subway franchise - slots that franchisees can use to come up with their own sandwich ideas."', '"Limits,True,Perception"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Higher unemployment generally bodes well for franchising. People are looking for a new opportunity, and people who have jobs are a little less confident they\'ll always have a job."', '"Opportunity,Looking,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'Most of the people we sign on as development agents commit to goals they don\'t believe are possible.', '"Believe,Goals,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"If you treat people nicely, and you allow them to fulfill a role that is satisfying for them, they\'ll accomplish a lot, and they\'ll enjoy their work."', '"Work,Treat,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"We give great value for our franchisees: They can build a store for well under $200,000. And we have extremely simple operating systems. The preparation is mostly done in front of the customer. That simplicity is really what attracts our Subway franchise. You see it, and you can do it."', '"Great,Simple,You Can Do It"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"I don\'t have any interest in cashing out or leaving the business or doing something else. I just love Subway, and I want to keep focusing on the company for the benefit of all our franchise owners. So I\'m kind of like married to the job."', '"Love,Business,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"To a large extent, we\'re working hard to fulfill the consumer demand for Subway sandwiches."', '"Hard,Consumer,Subway"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Because the stores worked, franchisees wanted to build more stores. If your model works, folks who are happy with it will buy out the ones who aren\'t happy."', '"Will,Happy,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"A lot of stuff happens daily when you\'re running a company like Subway. If you get too happy about some things or too unhappy about others, you get worn out. It\'s best if you can pace yourself a little bit more."', '"Best,Daily,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'Subway is a real point of pride. We have influenced the way people eat.', '"Pride,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"In some markets, we don\'t have a lot of room to expand. We\'ve done studies of store density and essentially found our more dense markets have more than one store per 15,000 people."', '"People,Done,Room"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"You have to realize that the customer really is king. People who go into more established businesses probably have to be careful not to be casual about that. When you have a brand-new business, and nobody knows who you are, you know you have to work really hard for your customers."', '"Work,Business,King"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I was able to solve enough big problems along the way that the sheriff didn\'t come along and put the \'bankruptcy\' sign up.', '"Problems,Way,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I guess that\'s one of the benefits of being sick. Your wife lets you have a big-screen TV in the living room.', '"Wife,Living Room,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"The people who come to work deserve to be paid properly, and there\'s no excuse. I could understand someone making a small error, but sometimes people make systematic errors, and that\'s not right."', '"Work,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"If I were in charge of the government, I would index the minimum wage to inflation, so that way, everybody knows what they can count on."', '"Government,Way,Inflation"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"I was 17 years old when I built the first store... A very simple, basic store with a basic counter - not very much equipment, all purchased second-hand. And the menu was very simple."', '"Simple,Menu,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"For a franchise system to work well, you really need people with an entrepreneurial mind-set because, while you have a large, overarching system that everybody has to work with, a lot of local issues have to be handled."', '"Work,People,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Back when we started, people didn\'t even know what a submarine sandwich was. The product was only sold in a few markets."', '"People,Back,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Everybody who goes through the business will make mistakes. The big question is how big will the mistakes be? How fast will they learn from the mistakes, and how quickly will they get the business in the correct direction?"', '"Business,Direction,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"You start a business, and you really don\'t have much of a budget."', '"Business,Start,Budget"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"In a typical situation, it\'s going to take pretty close to a year to get your location in, get your permits, and then get open."', '"Situation,Your,Open"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'There are so many ingredients that are approved for use. You can\'t be an expert on all of them.', '"Expert,Use,Ingredients"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"When I started in the business, the minimum wage was $1.25. I\'ve seen an enormous number of wage increases. Basically, it applies evenly to everyone in the business."', '"Business,Everyone,Minimum Wage"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"It\'s tough for people to get into business, especially a small business."', '"Business,Tough,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'The payroll tax is affecting sales. It\'s causing sales declines.', '"Payroll,Tax,Sales"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Six months after we started, in 1964, there was a day when we sold only seven sandwiches. If we\'d taken all the money from the register, we couldn\'t have paid an employee, much less the food or the rent or all that. It could have been a turning point. We could have given up."', '"Money,Food,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"There\'s huge access to information. If you need to learn something, you can go on the Internet and learn very quickly. You can reach across miles and miles to find companies that can assist you."', '"Internet,Information,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"I watch \'Shark Tank,\' of course. It\'s very entertaining. I think it\'s actually good to help people think about the business they might start, and sometimes you get encouraged by looking at someone going into business and saying, \'Hey, I could do that.\'"', '"Business,Good,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I don\'t have much of a bucket list. I don\'t have a lot of needs and desires.', '"Needs,Bucket,Much"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'You have to be able to communicate the vision to the people in your organization so that they know where and how they should direct themselves on a day-to-day basis.', '"Vision,Organization,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Every time I come across learning items of interest, I\'ll send distribution voice mail to the appropriate group in the organization."', '"Time,Learning,Organization"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'We have always had many more franchisee candidates than available locations.', '"Always,More,Available"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"The United States is a huge market, and once you get rolling, you can replicate that model over and over pretty easily. Your supply lines are taken care of. You don\'t have technicians to deal with. You\'ve got your customer base."', '"Care,Your,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"When we first started the company, I didn\'t have any thoughts of franchising. We just had company-owned stores."', '"Thoughts,Company,First"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"When you\'re invested in your own business, you\'re going to run it better. When people are financially responsible for whether their store succeeds, they\'re going to have that kind of entrepreneurial spirit that\'s harder to get if headquarters is running things."', '"Business,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"If you have company-owned stores, you make 100 percent of the profit from each one, but you have less entrepreneurial spirit."', '"Spirit,Profit,Percent"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"We find that no matter what country we\'re in, if we hit the right economic notes and appeal to the mass market, we\'re able to build the business very, very rapidly."', '"Business,Country,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'Everybody eats three times a day; it\'s only a question of where they choose to eat. The longer-term trends are people eat out more often.', '"Day,People,Trends"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"In the U.S. and Canada, we have one store for every 12,000 people."', '"People,Canada,Store"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"In 1974, we began franchising. We didn\'t have any big thought process except that, \'OK, franchising will help us get to our goal of 32 stores and help us run stores farther away from home.\'"', '"Home,Process,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"I tell everybody there are only three things that we do. We build sales at the store level, we build profits at the store level, and we build more stores. The first two things go in tandem, of course. It\'s pretty tough to build profits without sales."', '"Tough,Three,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"After 39 years of business, I\'m still learning. I go through this every year -identifying new strategies that are extremely important."', '"Business,Learning,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"From my point of view, my job is just to work hard for our franchisees, so they can maintain the position they\'re in, and to grow market share."', '"Work,View,Grow"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"A couple times a year, I get in the car, and I\'ll drive 1,000 miles cross-country, going through side streets. I\'ll stay off the highways as much as possible. And I realize it\'s a huge country, and for us to be in so many places in the country is an amazing thing."', '"Car,Amazing,Drive"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'The franchisees are uniquely in touch at the local level. They see what\'s going on in their communities in a way we couldn\'t ever imagine.', '"Way,See,Touch"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'We\'re very much in the people business in that there are two important groups you have to work with: customers and employees.', '"Work,Business,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"You really have to understand this isn\'t a business where you sit in the back room and do calculations - you have to be very concerned about employees and customers, because that\'s really what\'s going to bring you success."', '"Success,Business,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"I know a lot of people at some point in their business careers decide they\'ll just cash in and do something else, but for some reason, I\'ve never had that feeling."', '"Business,People,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I made the first sandwich before entering college.', '"Sandwich,First,College"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I went to school because I was supposed to. I did pre-med because my mum thought it was a good idea.', '"Good,School,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Even if you set a long-term goal, that doesn\'t mean it\'s a straight-line journey. Often, there are problems and obstacles along the way."', '"Journey,Problems,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"How you handle the obstacles has a big impact on how you do. If you give up, then you obviously don\'t get there, but if you\'re persistent, and you keep thinking of new ways to approach the business, you\'re more likely to reach your goal."', '"Business,Thinking,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"You could have everything right but be in the wrong place. You think your business is no good, but really, the problem is your place is no good."', '"Business,Good,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"By and large, we\'re a bread-eating culture. People like sandwiches. We don\'t really over-think that one."', '"Culture,People,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"Back in the early days of international, everybody wanted to customize the menu for every place."', '"Back,Place,Menu"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', '"We have salads, some other beverages. But in reality, it\'s still fundamentally the same business. The most likely thing the next person will buy is a sandwich and a soft drink. After a half-century of glacial change, we\'re still pretty much the same business."', '"Change,Business,Reality"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea5', 'I don\'t think I ever dreamt of going into business. No one in my family was in business.', '"Family,Business,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'That\'s your best friend and your worst enemy - your own brain.', '"Best,Brain,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"If you wanna know how not secure you are, just take a look around. Nothing\'s secure. Nothing\'s safe. I don\'t hate technology, I don\'t hate hackers, because that\'s just what comes with it, without those hackers we wouldn\'t solve the problems we need to solve, especially security."', '"Technology,Hate,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"It\'s amazing how, over time, a person\'s perspective can be altered."', '"Time,Amazing,Perspective"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"Everybody loves the underdog, and then they take an underdog and make him a hero and they hate him. But as long as they can knock you back down, it seems like if you\'re an underdog again, and things do surface, and they think this is real, \'these guys\' intentions are genuine and sincere,\' it seems like they will embrace you again."', '"Hero,Hate,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When I look back on my knee-jerk reactions now, I realize I should have just taken a breath."', '"Look,Back,Realize"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I\'ve been around golf my whole life. My father did it all the time, and I resented him for it. But a couple years ago I picked up a golf club and I understood the physics of it. If anyone knows anything about golf, it\'s that once you hit a few shots, you\'ll become addicted."', '"Life,Time,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Sometimes it\'s about less is more. It\'s about the seed. Thinking about this gigantic tree that you think is so beautiful but it started with this just seed.', '"Beautiful,Thinking,Tree"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I don\'t hate technology, I don\'t hate hackers, because that\'s just what comes with it, without those hackers we wouldn\'t solve the problems we need to solve, especially security."', '"Technology,Hate,Hackers"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'When you reminisce aren\'t the times that someone\'s forcing you to reminisce. You reminisce other times in your life.', '"Life,Reminisce,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'My life. The life I\'m living that\'s where all my inspiration comes from. Real life experiences.', '"Life,My Life,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'To walk around with an ego is a bad thing. To have confidence in yourself is a great thing.', '"Great,Walk,Confidence"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"There\'s an insecure part of me that comes out of me, I get nervous. I don\'t know why, I wish I could overcome it because it gives me an anxiety feeling."', '"Me,Know,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Prague is a dark place.', '"Dark,Place,Dark Place"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I stopped predicting the future a long time ago.', '"Future,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I loved the Cure and Bauhaus and the Smiths. The people in my town weren\'t privy to that kind of music and I got abused. I discovered the microphone to get out some of that angst.', '"Music,People,Loved"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m an actor\'s director. I love it when talented actors can bring characters to life.', '"Life,Love,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I don\'t fight people for fun.', '"Fight,Fun,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I was a kid who got picked on in school, and now the guys beating up those kids were wearing red caps and using my music to fuel that aggression. But if they listen to the lyrics, the aggression is targeted at them."', '"Music,School,Red"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When life was worrying about a car payment or a rent payment and a bill, you\'re so consumed with that, you really don\'t have time to know yourself. That\'s surviving and getting by."', '"Life,Car,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I love electronic music, and I love drum and bass."', '"Love,Music,Drum"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m in touch with the social networks and stuff.', '"Touch,Social,Stuff"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m a real director.', '"Real,Director"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I won\'t deny a song or a melody. I can\'t deny it.', '"Song,Melody,Deny"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m a romantic guy.', '"Romantic,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"Once you get in a position where your rent is taken care of and you do have a job, you really get to deal with yourself and really become one with yourself. And you wake to your mind every day. That\'s your best friend and your worst enemy - your own brain."', '"Best,Brain,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Sometimes I feel like I used to be a person that liked to express himself a lot and put my feelings out there.', '"Feel,Feelings,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Being in front of all these people staring at you and it helps you to dig down and become more emotional and get lost in it as you\'re feeding on people\'s energy.', '"Energy,Lost,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When Wes came back to Limp Bizkit, we really wanted to do something different. We wanted to make a core record that we didn\'t care who liked or who disliked."', '"Care,Back,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m definitely on the incline to a peak.', '"Peak,Definitely,Incline"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m a sentimental guy.', '"Guy,Sentimental"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m always looking for new talent.', '"Talent,Looking,New"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'One of the things that was confusing about Limp Bizkit to some people is that our tastes were very different.', '"People,Some People,Confusing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Our music has always been instant reactive and I guess taking our time to absorb things and say what you really want to say could be much more offensive than anything we\'ve ever done.', '"Time,Music,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I love finding EPs for bands that you just discover.', '"Love,Just,Finding"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I\'m a sensitive guy; I respond to things that make my eyes well up a little bit, or make me root for people. I find the human condition interesting."', '"Eyes,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"My Web site, everything I write in there is from me."', '"Me,Everything,Web"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When you say something is very different to a core base that expects heavy music from you or very aggressive music, everybody tends to go, \'Oh, they\'re gonna get mellow, they\'re gonna get soft.\'"', '"Music,Aggressive,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'There\'s definitely an obstacle in developing a brand for yourself that people can rely on when you\'re so eclectic.', '"Yourself,People,Eclectic"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"People evolve and grow, and life is fascinating and fun and tragic."', '"Life,Grow,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"It\'s not about how much movement you do, how much interaction there is, it just reeks of credibility if it\'s real. If it\'s contrived, it seems to work for a while for the people who can\'t filter out the real and unreal."', '"Work,People,Filter"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I do think that some bands seem to be dabbling in the rock-hip-hop world and are not necessarily serious about it.', '"World,Serious,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I think they\'d rather us follow our hearts and I hope that\'s what some people will understand.', '"Hope,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m an actor\'s director.', '"Actor,Director"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I love it when talented actors can bring characters to life. Anybody who wears their feelings on their sleeve and has a harder, crusty shell - like I do - is definitely protecting an inner sensitivity."', '"Life,Love,Feelings"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"There\'s some people who are not understanding what Limp Bizkit is about. But, then again, who am I to tell people what they can use art for or how they can interpret it?"', '"Art,People,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I wouldn\'t support Limp Bizkit being on some snuff backyard brawling, fighting contest."', '"Fighting,Support,Backyard"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I love jazz music and sad music. I\'m a sentimental guy. I\'m a romantic guy.', '"Love,Sad,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I\'m 38 years old and Limp Bizkit is just something I do. If I was a painter, it would just be a type of painting I make."', '"Painting,Old,Just Be"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'And touring is difficult when everybody\'s heads aren\'t in the same place.', '"Difficult,Place,Same"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"As much as I want to go out and tour every single day and I\'m ready to rip it right now, there\'s five people in the band, there\'s five people who\'ve evolved and grown and there\'s five people who have to get on the same page and want the same things, and it takes a lot to tour."', '"Day,People,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"Emotionally, I was affected a lot by Rage Against the Machine, not specifically the literal intention of the words or what it was about, but the feel, the sound, those phrases that got me."', '"Me,Words,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m the same guy at that podium preaching to the people on every single song. I\'m not doing a dance for you on another song. It\'s all a direct assault.', '"Song,People,Dance"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I want to clear my mind a little bit and give my mind a little bit of time to breathe so I can pinpoint or at least nail down feelings I\'m having and that I\'ve had for the last however long. I need to nail them down long enough to actually write about and elaborate on them.', '"Time,Mind,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"Anybody who wears their feelings on their sleeve and has a harder, crusty shell - like I do - is definitely protecting an inner sensitivity."', '"Feelings,Who,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'ve always wanted to make movies.', '"Movies,Always,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When you\'re a kid, you see your parents reading the newspaper and you\'re like, \'God, why are they reading the newspaper?\' When you\'re young, you\'re not reading the newspaper. But there comes a time in your life when the newspaper\'s cool."', '"Life,Cool,God"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"You know, in my music career there was a moment where the irony was just so heavy. There were people in my audience that were the reason I developed neuroses. These people that tortured my life were using my art, my poetry, as fuel for them, to torture other people."', '"Life,Art,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I was a kid who got picked on in school and got beat up by popular, athletic soccer-type people."', '"People,School,Beat"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I think ever since I was preteen I wanted to direct movies and tell stories.', '"Movies,Tell,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"For someone in my position, there\'s opportunities to be anything you want to be, even if you shouldn\'t be eligible, and I think that\'s left a bad taste in a lots of financers\' and studios\' mouths. Just cause someone\'s popular at one thing, letting them do the other isn\'t always the right thing."', '"The Right Thing,Bad,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"When I go to shows, I\'m really looking forward to hearing the songs I know. I don\'t like it when a band tries to expose me to new stuff."', '"Me,Looking Forward,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m OCD beyond comparison.', '"Beyond,Comparison"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I don\'t think my name would necessarily draw people to come see the movie. It might hurt the movie, honestly."', '"People,See,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I didn\'t want to do a throwaway, mindless movie with fart jokes just to make 6-year-olds laugh. I want to provide my children with some substance."', '"Children,Laugh,Fart"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I am not a hater.', '"I Am,Am"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Sometimes you feel like it\'s cursed when something takes so long to come out and you don\'t know if it\'s going to really come out.', '"Long,Feel,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"Directing a movie is serious, it\'s not a joke."', '"Serious,Joke,Directing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'Directing a film is a lot of work.', '"Work,Film,Directing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I want to make timeless movies.', '"Movies,Want,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m obsessed by film. I\'m obsessed with music and producing and making things happen.', '"Music,Things Happen,Film"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I\'m my own salesman. I can\'t let anybody do anything for me.', '"Me,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I made a lot mistakes that I\'m grateful for, because I won\'t make them again and I won\'t let my artists make them, or I\'ll tell them, \'Don\'t do this.\' A lot of them still make them anyway, but you can\'t be told things when you\'re doing your own thing."', '"Grateful,Mistakes,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', '"I usually find several ways to express myself: different moods, different days, different voices, different things, \'I\'m lighthearted today, I\'m gonna do this.\'"', '"Today,Myself,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I have always been Fred Durst and I\'ve always been me.', '"Me,Always,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea6', 'I love collaborating.', '"Love,I Love,Collaborating"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Everything will be tokenized and connected by a blockchain one day.', '"Day,Will,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Make no mistake - Ethereum would never have existed without Bitcoin as a forerunner. That said, I think Ethereum is ahead of Bitcoin in many ways and represents the bleeding edge of digital currency."', '"Bitcoin,Mistake,Digital"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"There is nothing that Bitcoin can do which Ethereum can\'t. While Ethereum is less battle-tested, it is moving faster, has better leadership, and has more developer mindshare."', '"Leadership,Bitcoin,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'The ability to easily buy and sell Bitcoin has been a really key factor in accelerating Bitcoin adoption.', '"Bitcoin,Ability,Buy"', '2023-05-29 12:06:00', '2023-05-29 12:06:00'),
	('400813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Ethereum has taken what was a four-function calculator of a programming language in Bitcoin and turned it into a full-fledged computer.', '"Bitcoin,Language,Programming"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Working on a token is similar to working on a startup: higher risk and lower initial impact but higher upside potential. How core protocol work is best funded beyond the initial Ethereum Foundation endowment is an open question, but likely further out."', '"Work,Best,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'The Internet will continue to be valuable so long as it is the most efficient mechanism for transferring data. Bitcoin\'s value is the same: It will remain as long as it is the most efficient mechanism for transferring ownership.', '"Bitcoin,Long,Value"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Just as the Internet brought the cost of disseminating information down by an order of magnitude, bitcoin brings the cost of transferring ownership down by an order of magnitude."', '"Bitcoin,Internet,Information"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Bitcoin\'s value is the same: It will remain as long as it is the most efficient mechanism for transferring ownership.', '"Bitcoin,Long,Value"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Bitcoin is valuable as a currency because of the economic efficiencies the bitcoin network is already creating as transactions flow over it. As with the Internet, more applications will flourish which will make the bitcoin network, and thus bitcoin as a currency, valuable."', '"Bitcoin,Internet,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Just like mutations to DNA in biological organisms allow for evolution through natural selection, forking lets us run multiple experiments in parallel where the strongest versions survive."', '"Survive,DNA,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Bitcoin has a core technological innovation: The ability to publicly verify ownership, instantly transfer that ownership, and do so without the need for a trusted third party."', '"Bitcoin,Innovation,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Bitcoin is inherently international, and one of its great promises is it enables cross-border payments in a more efficient way."', '"Great,Bitcoin,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"When you drill down, blockchains are really a shared version of reality everyone agrees on. So whether it\'s a fully immersive VR experience, augmented reality, or even Bitcoin or Ethereum in the physical world as a shared ledger for our \'real world,\' we\'ll increasingly trust blockchains as our basis for reality."', '"Trust,Experience,Reality"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Scaling is multidimensional. Different methods address different things.', '"Things,Scaling,Different"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Ethereum will be a first-class citizen on Coinbase.', '"Will,Ethereum,Citizen"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"When the actual Bitcoin network launched in 2009, no one knew about it, and many of those who did thought it would surely fail. Just to make sure the thing worked, the scripting language in Bitcoin was intentionally extremely restrictive."', '"Bitcoin,Language,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Private funding was one of the first methods used when MIT funded Bitcoin core developers Gavin Andresen, Wladimir van der Laan, and Cory Fields in 2015."', '"Bitcoin,First,Fields"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"If you are going to store your e-wallet on your own server, don\'t keep your e-wallet on your desktop, and make sure you use encryption. If you lose your computer, your bitcoins are lost forever."', '"Lose,Lost,Forever"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"For the foreseeable future, I\'m all about building blockchain-based decentralized services."', '"Future,Building,About"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"When Coinbase was starting, we thought we were seeing the birth of something that was really important - what I would almost describe as the future fabric of society - the system for who we are - our identities, what we own, our assets."', '"Future,Society,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'OpenAI is doing important work by releasing tools which promote AI to be developed in the open. Compute power is largely produced by NVIDIA and Intel and still relatively expensive but openly purchasable. Blockchains may be the key final ingredient by providing massive pools of open training data.', '"Work,Power,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"When the Bitcoin white paper emerged in 2008, it was completely revolutionary. The amount of concepts that had to come together in just the right way - computer science, cryptography, and economic incentives - was astonishing."', '"Science,Together,Bitcoin"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Sales conducted on-chain through smart contracts couldn\'t really be done before Ethereum, which is why they are a newer concept. I think this style will become the most common over time."', '"Time,Smart,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"While it may seem scarier in the earlier days, I think ultimately the blockchain creates a safer world."', '"World,Blockchain,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Forks often arise from differences of opinion in the direction of a project. And tokens are increasingly a mechanism for voting on changes to their protocols. Since the point of a fork is to try a new path, the new fork may not want to port all of the prior holders opposed to trying the new path the fork was created to take."', '"Path,Direction,New"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"AIs are only as good as the data they are trained on. And while many of the tech giants working on AI, like Google and Facebook, have open-sourced some of their algorithms, they hold back most of their data."', '"Good,Back,AI"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Working on Ethereum could be similar to working at a Google: lower risk with broad impact right away. Working on a token is similar to working on a startup: higher risk and lower initial impact but higher upside potential.', '"Impact,Right,Google"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"At the end of the day, what\'s going to make bitcoin successful is more people making more interesting things, just like the beginning of the Internet."', '"End Of The Day,Bitcoin,Internet"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"As with early internet startups, some token models don\'t make sense. For every 1 huge hit, there will be 3 minor successes and 100 failures, so we shouldn\'t be surprised when some fail."', '"Internet,Will,Early"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'The Internet had a core innovation that made it valuable: The ability to disseminate data over a distributed network in a way that was significantly cheaper than the prior methods.', '"Internet,Way,Innovation"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'AIs are only as good as the data they are trained on.', '"Good,Data,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"At GDAX, we want to see new protocols and their tokens flourish."', '"New,See,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"To create an open protocol which helps coordinate resources towards a common goal, the resources need to be known at some level in the same way a lot of of data on the web needs to be public for it to be traversable and useful."', '"Way,Create,Data"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'AIs trained on open data are more likely to be neutral and trustworthy instead of biased by the interests of the corporation who created and trained them.', '"Data,Open,More"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Blockchains are digital organisms. As organisms evolve through changes in their DNA, blockchain protocols evolve through changes in their code. And like biological organisms, the most adaptive blockchains will be the ones that survive and thrive."', '"Will,Digital,Thrive"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Public crowdfunding still suffers from a tragedy of the commons problem. Everyone will want the benefit of the crowdfunded efforts but is incentivized to sit on the sidelines and hope others chip in.', '"Hope,Will,Tragedy"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'The self-driving car revolution was kicked off by The \'DARPA\' Grand Challenge to make an autonomous car traverse 132 mi. of a desert.', '"Car,Challenge,Revolution"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Not having sub-governance would be like anyone who owns USD being able to walk into a Google shareholder meeting and voting without owning Google stock just because Google shares happen to be denominated in USD.', '"Walk,Just Because,Google"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Ethereum may make monetary policy decisions like, \'Let\'s do 1% inflation to support the ongoing development of the Ethereum protocol.\' A token built on Ethereum might want to do the same."', '"Support,Development,Inflation"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Tokens align incentives between developers, contributors, users, and investors. They allow everyone who wants to contribute to a project early the opportunity to get in on the ground floor."', '"Opportunity,Project,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"I\'d guess blockchains will be the full-blown backbone of virtual worlds - the system for currency, assets, identity, even governance - before doing the same in the \'real world.\' Which is where I think we will end up in the real world eventually; it\'s just a matter of which goes first and how long until it\'s the case for both."', '"World,Long,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"Redistributing tokens is a balancing act. In most cases, forks probably want to keep ownership for users constant so users have at least the same incentives to use the new fork as the historical one."', '"New,Act,Historical"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'I think the whole narrative of blockchain without bitcoin will amount to very little.', '"Bitcoin,Will,Blockchain"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'The scripting language in Bitcoin is important because it is what makes Bitcoin \'programmable money\'. Within each Bitcoin transaction is the ability to write a little program.', '"Money,Bitcoin,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"People far too often associate derivatives markets with mere speculation, but there are very legitimate businesses that need derivatives to protect themselves against risk."', '"People,Need,Far"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'I think it\'s fundamentally a good sign that more and more professional traders and market makers are providing liquidity to the whole ecosystem. It allows people to move much larger quantities of digital currency more quickly than they would if that were not the case.', '"Good,People,Digital"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"The fundamentals of the token model are valuable and powerful. They allow communities to govern themselves, their economics, and rally a community in powerful ways that will allow open systems to flourish in a way that was previously impossible."', '"Community,Impossible,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"We are on our way to blockchains as the fabric of society - the system for what we own (assets), who we are (identity), how we make decisions (governance), and more in an increasingly digital world. It\'s going to be a wild ride."', '"Society,Ride,World"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"There\'s been a myth perpetuated where people think, \'I need to go into consulting, banking, finance, law, or medicine to make a consistently reasonable amount of money.\' People are now realizing that\'s not the case."', '"Money,Finance,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', '"The best engineered organisms can outpace others, even if they start smaller or later."', '"Best,Start,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea7', 'Developer mindshare is the most important thing to have in digital currency.', '"Important,Digital,Currency"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', '"Living in Chicago as a country boy, basically, and going to college made a very big impact on me."', '"Me,Country,Impact"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'I don\'t put my name on stuff.', '"Name,Stuff,Put"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'I just like my independence and freedom to come and go and not have an entourage.', '"Freedom,Independence,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', '"I\'m not a billionaire, and I\'m not a mogul."', 'Billionaire', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'I\'m a retired media executive.', '"Media,Executive,Retired"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', '"I would go on the record with my respect for Mike Madigan, which will probably upset a lot of friends. He\'s enormously skillful at what he does. The only speakers of any House who survive are the ones who can keep their majority and keep everyone going largely in the same direction. Mike Madigan is superb at that."', '"Respect,Direction,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'I am not the progressive Koch brother.', '"I Am,Brother,Progressive"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', '"I am a basic social activist with small-business experience, and you go where you need to go."', '"Experience,I Am,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'I am not Richard Branson.', '"I Am,Am,Richard"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'Consolidation is so overwhelming. Someone who has one or two stations doesn\'t have much clout.', '"Someone,Two,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', '"The process of coming out was critical to getting where we are today: coming out to our friends, our family, our co-workers, God forbid, to our clients."', '"Family,God,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea8', 'Part of our history includes the long struggle to pass the Chicago Human Rights Ordinance.', '"History,Struggle,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"One regret I have is that I did not learn more about what was happening very early, so that I could have tried to stop people from engaging in illegal activities."', '"Regret,People,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', 'The Nixon years were trying. They honed my judgment for everything I did later on. The experience also illustrated for me the importance of training young lawyers properly.', '"Experience,Me,Training"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"Morgan, Lewis is a very large firm now, but it was not quite as big then. It was exciting for an associate in those days, because you got good and varied assignments and terrific training."', '"Good,Training,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', 'This drama between Dean and Ehrlichman took place while I was trying to give the contents to the FBI.', '"Drama,Place,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"But look, you did not have to be well versed in politics to know that some stupid things were going on. It is the counsel\'s job to stop them, and instead the coverup was created."', '"Politics,Stupid,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"Dean had just come from seeing his lawyer. That was the first time that I found out that he had consulted a lawyer. He wanted to tell me what he thought was going on, but he was writing it down as if my house was bugged. He acted like everything was bugged."', '"Time,Me,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', 'It was frightening because it was the first time I had gotten a sense of how serious the problem was. It became clear from his notes that he felt the president himself was involved.', '"Time,First Time,Serious"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', 'I\'m still friendly with Dean. He still calls me on the phone from time to time. John Dean was fired and later ended up spending some time in prison for his role in Watergate.', '"Time,Me,Prison"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"It is hard for people outside the White House to understand the constant daily problems and issues that come up that require the president\'s attention, but he can not let himself get too personally involved."', '"Daily,Problems,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"It became evident to me that there was a very serious political element at work. I know that the term impeachment was bandied about. I do not believe, however, that the word was used with the ferocity it was more recently or that it was in the Nixon years."', '"Work,Political,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"The last eight years have created a lot of deep-seated hostility. People take political decisions very personally, and today there is a constant, ongoing attack, with one side or the other being maligned."', '"Today,Political,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fea9', '"Soon after I returned to private practice, former Supreme Court Chief Justice Warren Burger called me one day."', '"Justice,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"One of the things I particularly enjoyed doing was taking raw sound from locations during the film, like the candy machine, and writing pieces of music to go with them, which is totally unnecessary within the context of the film, because they have their own logic."', '"Music,Logic,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"You could say that everything the musicians have learned and known over the years, all of their technical resources, are in a dialogue with the things they are discovering every time, as if it was the first time."', '"Time,First Time,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'There\'s an awful lot of resources that can be drawn upon in an improvised music concert.', '"Music,Resources,Concert"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"Chris Cutler was kind enough to offer his company as an umbrella, so now I can have all my back catalogue under one roof as it were, and it has the same feeling as with Daniel; this is a matter between friends rather than businessmen."', '"Back,Company,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"We play melodic music, we play songs, we play all kinds of things and when you improvise you don\'t just shut out different languages, you use all the languages that you have."', '"Music,Things,Use"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"We went through this business of me writing out all the parts for these old songs from Gravity and Speechless and we\'d been performing that, but we don\'t do that any more."', '"Business,Me,Old Songs"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'Improvised music involves a lot of intuition and I like developing intuition.', '"Music,Intuition,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"As an improviser I\'m now pretty comfortable with trios, so I\'m thinking of working up to quartets."', '"Thinking,Comfortable,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"I think things changed as a result of a certain perception of our politics. When we went through our zealous, self-righteous period it didn\'t exactly win us any friends."', '"Politics,Result,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'We played some gigs in Switzerland a couple of weeks ago and it was the first time I really felt the group was really a band in the sense of something I could write for.', '"Time,First Time,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"There are always things to examine. What\'s great is not feeling that I have to refuse any of them. Maybe no good from a PR perspective, but from the point of view of everyday life, it keeps things interesting."', '"Life,Good,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"The totality of a record is usually beyond ones ability to imagine when you start working on it, but the component parts are, usually, fairly clear one way or another."', '"Way,Start,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"Some things don\'t wind up sounding like you\'d expect, which is just as well."', '"Wind,Well,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"Not necessarily in one concert, but they\'re all there to be used if you want to use them."', '"Use,Want,Concert"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"It\'s like learning a language; you can\'t speak a language fluently until you find out who you are in that language, and that has as much to do with your body as it does with vocabulary and grammar."', '"Learning,Body,Language"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'If you write songs you have an idea how they\'re going to sound.', '"Sound,Going,How"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"I write with a mouse, because it has no psychological associations or memories or habits associated with it."', '"Memories,Because,Mouse"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'I think that one of the things that influences me most as a composer is to what extent I can deconstruct and reconstruct the material that I\'m working with.', '"Me,I Can,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"I remember playing football dressed in peculiar costumes with some friends in France and laughing so hard we couldn\'t even stand up, let alone kick the ball."', '"Alone,Football,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', 'I don\'t know if I\'m striving for anything that I can put into words.', '"Words,Know,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"And so many of the kinds of labels you get stuck with don\'t really tell the story; Progressive, Art Rock, Noise Music, Downtown - it ends up being a struggle to stay out of debates that other people are having around you."', '"Art,Music,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaa', '"Well, I think music for kids is never anything but experimental is it?"', '"Music,Never,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I\'m going to be wearing the Stryker hat because I\'m a walking testimonial to the fact that you can get your knee replaced and still play at a really high level and get your life back.', '"Life,Hat,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"Augusta is a very unique golf course. It\'s a long hitters\' course; main reason is because the greens are so severe, and the areas where they put the pin is such a small area. The little plateaus and undulations mean it\'s incredibly important to be close to that pin so you can be aggressive."', '"Long,Unique,Aggressive"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"You worked your paper route, mowed the lawn, then played golf all day."', '"Day,Golf,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I don\'t want to go out there and show up. I hate losing. Everybody hates losing. But I hate losing.', '"Hate,Losing,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I would say that my downswing mirrors the path of my backswing pretty closely.', '"Path,Pretty,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"My career progressed slowly. Real slow at a time. The irony of it was I had the best part of my career between when I was 45 and 49 years old. That\'s when most people are in their twilight, waiting to get to the Champions Tour. And that\'s when I made most of my hay."', '"Best,Time,Waiting"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I would agree to some extent that on the Champions Tour that there is a greater premium on putting than the regular tour because of the course setups.', '"Because,Agree,Would"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'People are going to paying attention to him whether they love him or hate him. So I think Tiger is a huge focus point on a stage that is as little as golf.', '"Love,Focus,Hate"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"We have two tractor-trailer rigs on the Tour. One is a therapy truck, and one is a workout truck. If everything is going well, you\'re walking in the workout truck, and when things aren\'t going well, you\'re walking in the therapy truck."', '"Walking,Everything,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I don\'t want to rest on my laurels. I still feel like I\'m learning a lot about the golf game and the swing. There are so many different little facets of golf that there is always something to learn.', '"Learning,Game,Rest"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', 'I still pinch myself that I had the career that I had.', '"Myself,Still,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"I\'m not here just to walk two rounds or four rounds and just show up. I want to be able to be competitive, and I truly believe I can still be competitive when I\'m playing well and feeling good."', '"Good,Walk,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"The PGA Tour has a lot of interaction with our military, and I\'ve grown to have an incredible respect for our troops who are coming home with these horrific injuries, as well as any organization that can not only help them get healed up, but help them get integrated back into society."', '"Respect,Home,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"Stryker was a company that allowed me, when I had my knee replaced and I got the Stryker GetAroundKnee put in, to get my career back and get my life back."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"A couple of weeks before the 1992 Houston Open, I was probably as low as I could get confidence-wise. I didn\'t think I was going to go any further, and then, out of nowhere, I won that week. That kind of got me going."', '"Me,Week,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feab', '"I had never heard of staph until I got it. Didn\'t really know what was. Still don\'t really know what it is, but I know you just don\'t want to have it."', '"Never,Know,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', 'Ignoring a child\'s disrespect is the surest guarantee that it will continue.', '"Disrespect,Will,Continue"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', 'Teenagers who are never required to vacuum are living in one.', '"Teen,Living,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', '"We must return optimism to our parenting. To focus on the joys, not the hassles; the love, not the disappointments; the common sense, not the complexities."', '"Love,Parenting,Focus"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', 'Taking a child to the toy store is the nearest thing to a death wish parents can have.', '"Death,Parents,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', 'A child who has never fantasized about having other parents is seriously lacking in imagination.', '"Imagination,Parents,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feac', '"The more we shelter children from every disappointment, the more devastating future disappointments will be."', '"Future,Disappointment,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fead', '"When I was a teenager, I wanted to be a portrait painter. As I got to be older, I realized that as a portrait painter I wouldn\'t be able to support a goldfish."', '"Support,Portrait,Able"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fead', '"I decided to take a stab at acting. I entered the American Academy of Dramatic Art, where one teacher told me I\'d never make it - I was too tall."', '"Art,Teacher,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fead', 'I love making puns.', '"Love,Puns,Making"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"As a military pilot and a test pilot, handling unusual situations and aircraft malfunctions was part of the business."', '"Business,Pilot,Test"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', 'My biggest emotion on Apollo 13 after the oxygen tank explosion was disappointment that we had lost the landing.', '"Disappointment,Lost,Oxygen"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"I think you jump into things without thinking ahead very much because I had never been in an airplane - even in a commercial airliner. I had never flown at all. I just wanted to be commissioned, to be a commissioned officer."', '"Thinking,Airplane,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"It does make it very clear, you know, what can happen if you do have... the right people, the right skill mix, that are trained and they\'re assembled in this team and they work together under the right leadership. You know, what a miracle can happen. And that\'s what was the case of Apollo 13."', '"Leadership,Work,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"I cycled on a crew assignment as the backup commander on Apollo 16 and would have flown Apollo 19 on a return mission to the moon. However, the last few missions of the Apollo Program were canceled for budgetary reasons. So I lost my second opportunity to land on the moon."', '"Opportunity,Moon,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"All at once the cockpit lit up with a sort of white glow because your entry was at 25,000 miles an hour and it was ionising some of the first particles of air you had. So it was kinda a little bit like being inside a weak neon bulb."', '"Glow,White,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', 'I immediately loved flying from my first flight and knew that in some way it was going to be a part of my future career!', '"Future,Way,Loved"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', 'Obviously I\'d like NASA to follow their charter - the exploration of our solar system and beyond. I\'d like to see people someday go to Mars.', '"People,See,Solar"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feae', '"I\'ve had a good career, some good experiences."', '"Good,Had,Career"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', 'No weapon formed against me shall prosper.', '"Me,Weapon,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"We sing inspirational songs, songs of praise and worship, and about how good and how big God is. We are magnifying the Lord."', '"Inspirational,God,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"I was in a marriage, and we didn\'t make it. So my hope is, through my music, I can help heal some relationships that may be headed in that direction."', '"Hope,Music,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"I think people really want to see the real because the world is portrayed at such a low level that if you come out with a real wholesome show, people don\'t want to see that anymore."', '"World,People,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"The Bible is a novel that\'s crazy... it has murder, it has victory it has mayhem, it has disaster, it has war, sanctification."', '"War,Bible,Victory"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"I believe I was born for this, to tell people about the Lord. I just wanted to find the best way that I could do it, and music, God graced me to be able to do it, and that was the way that I chose to be effective and tell people that the Lord loves them."', '"Best,God,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"I am just so appreciative of God\'s love. It\'s higher than any mountain, wider than any ocean, and wider than the whole universe. His love is just that amazing!"', '"Love,God,Amazing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feaf', '"Women are a key part of the sound of the groups that accompany male singers like Kirk Franklin, Israel Houghton, and myself."', '"Women,Myself,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'You can kill a revolutionary but you can never kill the revolution.', '"Never,Revolution,Revolutionary"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We\'re going to fight racism not with racism, but we\'re going to fight with solidarity. We say we\'re not going to fight capitalism with black capitalism, but we\'re going to fight it with socialism."', '"Black,Fight,Capitalism"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"I am the people, I\'m not the pig. You got to make a distinction. And the people are going to have to attack the pigs. The people are going to have to stand up against the pigs. That\'s what the Panthers is doing, that\'s what the Panthers are doing all over the world."', '"World,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"Let me just say: Peace to you, if you\'re willing to fight for it."', '"Peace,Fight,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"You have to understand that people have to pay a price for peace. If you dare to struggle, you dare to win."', '"Peace,Struggle,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'I believe I\'m going to die doing the things I was born to do. I believe I\'m going to die high off the people. I believe I\'m going to die a revolutionary in the international revolutionary proletarian struggle.', '"Struggle,Believe,Die"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"If you ever think about me, and you ain\'t gonna do no revolutionary act, forget about me. I don\'t want myself on your mind if you\'re not going to work for the people."', '"Work,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"Black people need some peace. White people need some peace. And we are going to have to fight. We\'re going to have to struggle. We\'re going to have to struggle relentlessly to bring about some peace, because the people that we\'re asking for peace, they are a bunch of megalomaniac warmongers, and they don\'t even understand what peace means."', '"Peace,Black,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We\'re not a racist organization, because we understand that racism is an excuse used for capitalism, and we know that racism is just - it\'s a byproduct of capitalism."', '"Organization,Capitalism,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"Everything would be alright if everything was put back in the hands of the people, and we\'re going to have to put it back in the hands of the people."', '"People,Hands,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We ain\'t gonna fight no reactionary pigs who run up and down the street being reactionary; we\'re gonna organize and dedicate ourselves to revolutionary political power and teach ourselves the specific needs of resisting the power structure, arm ourselves, and we\'re gonna fight reactionary pigs with international proletarian revolution."', '"Power,Fight,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"You can jail a revolutionary, but you can\'t jail the revolution."', '"Revolution,Jail,Revolutionary"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"With no education, you have neocolonialism instead of colonialism, like you\'ve got in Africa now and like you\'ve got in Haiti. So what we\'re talking about is there has to be an educational program. That\'s very important."', '"Education,Important,Colonialism"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'I\'m not afraid to say I\'m at war with the pigs.', '"War,Afraid,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"You can\'t build a revolution with no education. Jomo Kenyatta did this in Africa, and because the people were not educated, he became as much an oppressor as the people he overthrew."', '"Education,People,Revolution"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We might not be back. I might be in jail. I might be anywhere. But when I leave, you\'ll remember I said, with the last words on my lips, that I am a revolutionary. And you\'re going to have to keep on saying that. You\'re going to have to say that I am a proletariat; I am the people."', '"I Am,Words,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'A lot of people think the Breakfast for Children program is charity. But what does it do? It takes the people from a stage to another stage. Any program that\'s revolutionary is an advancing program. Revolution is change.', '"Change,Breakfast,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We say primarily that the priority of this struggle is class. That Marx and Lenin and Che Guevara and Mao Tse-Tung, and anybody else who ever said or knew or practiced anything about revolution, always said that a revolution is a class struggle."', '"Struggle,Always,Revolution"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'The Black Panther Party stood up and said that we don\'t care what anybody says. We don\'t think fighting fire with fire is best; we think you fight fire with water best.', '"Best,Black,Fire"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'A lot of people don\'t understand the Black Panthers Party\'s relationship with white mother country radicals.', '"Relationship,Black,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"People have to be armed to have power, you see."', '"Power,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"We do not support people who are anarchistic, opportunistic, adventuristic, and Custeristic."', '"Support,People,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"I went down to the prison in Menard, thinking we were the vanguard, but down there, I got down on my knees and listened and learned from the people."', '"Thinking,People,Prison"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', '"Yes, we do defend our office as we do defend our homes. This is a constitutional right everybody has, and nothing\'s funny about that. The only reason they get mad at the Black Panther Party when you do it is for the simple reason that we\'re political."', '"Funny,Black,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'I have a lot of respect for Martin Luther King. I think he was one of the greatest orators that the country ever produced.', '"Respect,King,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb0', 'We say that we will work with anybody and form a coalition with anybody that has revolution on their mind.', '"Work,Mind,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', 'Space isn\'t remote at all. It\'s only an hour\'s drive away if your car could go straight upwards.', '"Car,Space,Drive"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', 'Things are the way they are because they were the way they were.', '"Way,Because,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', 'I don\'t see the logic of rejecting data just because they seem incredible.', '"Logic,See,Data"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', '"There is a coherent plan in the universe, though I don\'t know what it\'s a plan for."', '"Universe,Know,Plan"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', 'Once I had learnt my twelve times table (at the age of three) it was downhill all the way.', '"Age,Way,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb1', '"The man who voyages strange seas must of necessity be a little unsure of himself. It is the man with the flashy air of knowing everything, who is always with it, that we should beware of."', '"Man,Air,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'The value of Eric Foner\'s \'The Fiery Trial\' lies in its comprehensive review of mostly familiar material; in its sensible evaluation of the full range of information already available about Abraham Lincoln and slavery; and in the deft thoroughness of its scholarship.', '"Value,Information,Review"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'We do ourselves a disservice when we self-servingly massage the record.', '"Massage,Ourselves,Record"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"I started out as a writer of fiction, but nobody wanted to publish my work as a young man. So I decided to put my interest in the narrative writing of biographies."', '"Work,Man,Nobody"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Words about Lincoln fill a small but ever-growing library.', '"Words,Library,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"I\'m not a Lincoln expert, rather a biographer who has had the pleasure of reading much of what has been written about him from his lifetime to this year of his bicentennial. Some advice: Don\'t try that unless you have at least five years available."', '"Advice,Pleasure,Expert"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"A recommendation to scholars: Write only one book about Lincoln; give it your best shot, and then move on."', '"Best,Your,Shot"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"Gore Vidal was a man of immense literary talent, some of which he used well, some of which he wasted."', '"Man,Talent,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"With all due respect to re-enactors, I consider the Civil War too tragic a subject to make a game of."', '"War,Respect,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"Lincoln is distinguished from every other president, with the exception of Jefferson, in that we can be certain that he wrote every word to which his name is attached."', '"Name,He,President"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"The challenge of a president himself struggling to find the conjunction between the right words and honest expression, a use of language that respects intellect, truth, and sincerity, has largely been abandoned."', '"Truth,Words,Sincerity"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'To give credit to Lincoln for moral progression seems beyond the facts and unnecessary for our appreciation of this arguably greatest of all American presidents.', '"Appreciation,Facts,Credit"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"Reading Edmund Morris\'s \'Colonel Roosevelt\' is a rewarding journey, as it must also have been for its author, who concludes his three-volume saga begun in 1980 with publication of \'The Rise of Theodore Roosevelt.\'"', '"Journey,Rise,Reading"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"\'Colonel Roosevelt\' is compelling reading, and Morris a brilliant biographer who practices his art at the highest level."', '"Art,Brilliant,Reading"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"In his life, Charles Dickens was like the rest of us, but maybe more so: another poor and wonderful soul attempting to deal with his and the world\'s pain and confusion in the best way he knew how."', '"Life,Best,Pain"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"Can a great artist be mean-spirited, grasping, harsh to his family, violent in his emotions, vindictive in his hatreds, an all-purpose scoundrel? If our test cases are the likes of Wagner, Picasso, and, let me say, Dickens, the answer is a resounding yes."', '"Family,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Is there really any relationship between artists\' personal conduct and their art? Certainly not.', '"Relationship,Art,Personal"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'It should be quite clear that it is possible for unpleasant people who are small in various ways other than in their artistic genius to produce great art. Art and morality have no necessary connection.', '"Art,Great,Connection"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Political history is not the only way to approach historical figures.', '"History,Political,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('400999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"I got to know Gore Vidal quite well, up front and personal: his magnificent strengths and his appalling, almost other-worldly weaknesses."', '"Know,Well,Personal"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Lincoln is a genius of language and a brilliant writer who deserves to be seen as part of the canon of great writers in American literature.', '"Great,Genius,Language"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"Obama is a very fine writer with an excellent command of language. His memoir \'Dreams From My Father\' is a fine book, but it will not rank as one of the great autobiographies."', '"Dreams,Great,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Lincoln was the Twain of our politics.', '"Politics,Our,Lincoln"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Serious biographies need to have a historical base in facts.', '"Facts,Serious,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"I first wrote a biography of Thomas Carlyle, and it turned out I loved writing biographies and had a talent for it. I believed I had a contribution to make."', '"Talent,Loved,First"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'I want to contribute to the culture and keep great writers alive by telling the stories of their lives.', '"Great,Culture,Alive"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', 'Myth and mythology often serve constructive and aspirational purposes. But they also do harm.', '"Serve,Myth,Mythology"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb2', '"The post-assassination Lincoln took on a greatly amplified importance to much of the American public, probably the president most deeply reviled in his lifetime and mostly highly regarded after his death."', '"Death,American,Importance"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb3', '"Physics is the most basic part of science and, of course, math. It gives you insight into everything - a foundation, I should say, to understand nature and the universe."', '"Nature,Science,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb3', '"Basic research is to work at the very edge, the very border of, of knowledge, and move that border forward. You look and look for new secrets, and you don\'t know where it\'s going to lead you."', '"Work,Knowledge,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb3', '"I used to ski across the vast white expanses of a quiet and lonely mountaintop. In the stillness and solitude... I pondered the mysteries of the universe, the planet, nature and of man. I\'m still pondering."', '"Nature,Man,Solitude"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb3', '"As we gain more knowledge about materials and processes in the universe, that could open up benefits that we can\'t even imagine. But you have to be willing to fund science without knowledge of the benefits."', '"Science,Knowledge,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb3', 'I had long planned to start a foundation. I wanted to do something with long-range benefit to humanity. Starting a business and making a lot of money doesn\'t make for a fulfilling life.', '"Life,Business,Money"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"If you have the feeling that something is wrong, don\'t be afraid to speak up."', '"Speak,Wrong,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"Every day in school, we said the pledge to the flag, \'with liberty and justice for all,\' and I believed all that."', '"Justice,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I don\'t even know how it is to have a home. I feel like an orphan or something.', '"Home,Feel,Orphan"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I lost everything when they put us in prison. I was an enemy alien, a man without a country."', '"Man,Lost,Alien"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"One person can make a difference, even if it takes forty years."', '"Make A Difference,Person,Difference"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I thought what the military was doing was unconstitutional.', '"Doing,Thought,Military"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'All of them turned their backs on me at that time because they thought I was a troublemaker.', '"Time,Me,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I was born in the U.S. This is my country.', '"Country,Born,I Was Born"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"It may take time to prove you\'re right, but you have to stick to it."', '"Time,Right,Prove"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'If anyone should do any pardoning. I should be the one pardoning the government for what they did to the Japanese-American people.', '"Government,People,Did"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I still remember, 40 years ago, when I was shackled and put in prison... Being an American citizen didn\'t mean a thing."', '"Remember,Prison,American"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I\'m Asian, so they assumed I\'m not an American and that I come from Japan. Restaurants would refuse to serve me, and places would refuse to give you a haircut."', '"Haircut,Me,American"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"As long as my record stands in federal court, any American citizen can be held in prison or concentration camps without a trial or a hearing."', '"Long,Prison,American"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"During the curfew, whoever went out, the people were watching you. Any Japanese home, there was some person figuring he\'s a good American citizen by doing his duty, and they were watching every move each family were doin\'. Or if they went out, they followed them to see where they were goin\'."', '"Family,Good,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"As a citizen of the United States, I am ready, willing, and able to bear arms for this country."', '"I Am,Country,Ready"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I was an American citizen, and I had as many rights as anyone else."', '"American,Rights,American Citizen"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"Before the war, my parents were very proud people. They\'d always talk about Japan and also about the samurai and things like that. Right after Pearl Harbor, they were just real quiet. They kept to themselves; they were afraid to talk about what could happen. I assume they knew that nothing good would come out of it."', '"War,Good,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I was really upset because I was branded as an enemy alien when I\'m an American.', '"Alien,Enemy,American"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"My folks were so worried about what they were going to do. All they can take was what they could carry with their hands. What they had for twenty-five years of building their business was going to go out the door, or they\'re going to lose it."', '"Business,Lose,Door"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I was just living my life, and that\'s what I wanted to do."', '"Life,My Life,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I didn\'t think that the government would go as far as to include American citizens to be interned without a hearing.', '"Government,American,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'I was very upset because I did not have a fair trial to prove my loyalty to this country.', '"Loyalty,Country,Upset"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', 'It takes a lot of money to hire an attorney.', '"Money,Hire,Lot"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"I was the third son, and the family tradition was my dad always favored the oldest child."', '"Family,Dad,Son"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb4', '"That was it - I lost my job... I was very discouraged. I wanted to be in defense work... I\'m an American, and I have nothin\' to do with Japan, and so it\'s sort of an insult to me."', '"Work,Me,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', '"You need to decide what problems, what opportunities, what projects you\'re going to work on."', '"Work,Problems,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'If I had been a bricklayer I\'d still have been a journeyman.', '"Still,Had,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'I think the ability to focus is a thread that runs through so-called successful people. And that\'s something that can be developed. It can be self-taught.', '"Focus,People,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'You can\'t work on 15 problems at the same time.', '"Work,Time,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', '"There were around 1,000 stores when I was made president."', '"President,Made,Around"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'We\'ve got a low turnover management group and executive group who\'ve grown up in the business.', '"Business,Management,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'I get a bit of a kick out of exporting private enterprise and incentives.', '"Kick,Get,Out"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', '"Work hard, use your common sense and don\'t be afraid to trust your instincts."', '"Work,Trust,Common Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb5', 'People who are employed in a way they don\'t like - my heart cries for them.', '"Heart,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I was fishing with director Frank Capra once and we talked about retirement.', '"Fishing,Retirement,Once"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'You\'d think people would regard you as an actor and you could play anything. But with TV they regard you almost as a member of the family.', '"Family,People,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m really not that rich. I really don\'t know how I got the reputation of being so loaded. Maybe my business manager started it. But I always say that I\'m just rich enough that I don\'t have to do a television series.', '"Business,Rich,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I just don\'t care to work that hard.', '"Work,Care,dont Care"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"You know, you can only play just so much golf or go fishing just so often."', '"Fishing,Know,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I never went to acting school; when someone expounds on motivation and all that stuff, I don\'t understand it. I was just lucky to be able to do what I did. When I started, people said I was very natural, which I guess is difficult for a lot of people to be."', '"Difficult,People,School"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"Being Scottish, I\'m probably a little tight, or as the Scots say, \'You\'re cautious with your money.\' I don\'t think that \'s the worst thing in the world to be."', '"Money,World,Worst"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Sometimes a writer writes scenes for people who just say \'Hi\' to indicate they\'re in love. I play those scenes very well.', '"Love,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"A lot of actors go crazy if they\'re not working, but I guess I\'m a little lazy."', '"Crazy,Lazy,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I\'m Scottish, so I took care of my money."', '"Money,Care,Scottish"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"June cooks, I cook and we have a girl who comes in to clean three days a week. We like that way of living. I suppose a lot of people think we can afford more, but we like it simple."', '"Simple,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Cooking is our hobby. We find recipes we like and then try to turn them into good meals. Most of the time our experimenting turns out pretty well. But sometimes we create lousy dinners.', '"Time,Good,Cooking"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'We\'re content to knock around the house.', '"House,Content,Knock"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I keep up to scratch on the sax.', '"Up,Keep,Scratch"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'We have a jam session at home every so often. That\'s one reason I bought a house with lots of ground around it the neighbors can\'t hear us play!', '"Home,Ground,House"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'A beautiful woman is the best investment in marriage a man can make. And anybody who advises otherwise is talking sheer nonsense.', '"Best,Marriage,Beautiful Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"Just because a woman is beautiful doesn\'t mean she can\'t be a good wife. If her beauty affects her personality, then it\'s her mentality that\'s at fault... not the tilt of her nose."', '"Beauty,Good,Personality"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"A man marries the most gorgeous girl he can find because It\'s human nature to want the best of anything. If other men admire her he likes that, too. We all work best under competition. After all, no one wants to face an egg beater across the breakfast table... or find a horror movie in his home when he doesn\'t even own a TV set."', '"Nature,Work,Best"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"Any woman can make herself beautiful. I see \'em do it every day in the studio... with make-up and hair styles and curves added, that is. Science can do anything."', '"Science,Beautiful,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I saw a clown knock the head off another clown and I thought it was the real thing. It scared me so much, I made my mother take me home and I\'ve dodged circuses ever since."', '"Home,Me,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I haven\'t the knack of being colorful.', '"Colorful,Being,Knack"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I wanted a good humored kind of show, a show without violence. I liked the idea behind \'My Three Sons,\' and I liked the people involved."', '"Good,People,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I like to hunt and fish, read and paint and play golf. And I can have a good time doing nothing. And, of course: be with my family."', '"Family,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'It\'s nice to be in a picture that\'s doing business.', '"Business,Picture,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"The Apartment\' was fun, but I enjoy comedy much more, and I feel I do it better."', '"Fun,Better,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I like hills and trees.', '"Like,Trees,Hills"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'The only award I ever got was the Popscar.', '"Award,Only,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"People look upon me primarily as a comedian. I\'m trying to get away from that, though I do like comedy."', '"Look,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I don\'t want the audience to tire of me too quickly. TV would be the fastest way to make them so sick of my face they\'d never want to see it again.', '"Face,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I would never do comedy on TV.', '"Comedy,Never,Would"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'A man can get old pretty fast if he doesn\'t keep his mind active.', '"Man,Mind,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"When we were doing \'My Three Sons,\' I appeared in the movie \'The Apartment.\' I played a married businessman who kept a mistress on the side and treated her rather poorly. It was a good movie and a good role, and I thought it would be fun. But you should have seen the letters of protest I got over that."', '"Good,Fun,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I want intelligence in my wife, but not too much she might see through me."', '"Intelligence,Wife,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"Seriously, I do not think that a marriage can be successful in which either the husband or the wife is far more intelligent than the other."', '"Marriage,Wife,Intelligent"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"Look, I don\'t do anything that these glamour guys do. The front pages never heard of me."', '"Look,Me,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I don\'t night-club, don\'t get into fights or scandals, don\'t own a yacht, don\'t play the horses, don\'t wear plaid overcoats, don\'t go to Hollywood parties, don\'t own a motorcycle, don\'t run back and forth to New York, don\'t go in for politics."', '"Politics,Motorcycle,New"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m dull.', 'Dull', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"If I spend a couple of hours practising on the driving range, my 10 handicap becomes a 12 by the time I get on the course."', '"Time,Driving,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Both Lily and I feel we have a responsibility to our kids and it\'s one we enjoy; we love being with them.', '"Love,Responsibility,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m an actor. That proves how lazy I am. It\'s foolish to take on any other jobs.', '"I Am,Lazy,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I never could understand why Leslie Fenton gave up a soft touch in front of the camera to move behind it.', '"Never,Camera,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I never wanted to be an actor. I only came to Hollywood to drive my mother out to visit my grandmother.', '"Drive,Never,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m not an actor. I\'m a personality.', '"Personality,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"When I read some of the things other movie people say about their work, I think I\'m in the wrong business. I don\'t have any of those deep thoughts. I\'m just myself."', '"Work,Business,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'There\'s a lack of tremendous pressure in the Disney studios. It\'s a pleasant place to be.', '"Pressure,Place,Pleasant"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"We\'ve talked about doing a reunion of \'My Three Sons,\' but I have an aversion to actors doing reunions."', '"Doing,Three,Reunion"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I was a star before I got more than $250 a week. Carole Lombard advised me how to get a raise. She said: \'Go to Palm Springs and stay there until they raise the ante.\' They were waiting to start a picture with me and I was scared they\'d forget me for someone else, but they came after me."', '"Waiting,Me,Picture"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I nrver make the front pages or the gossip columns.', '"Gossip,Front,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"If we can show the good side of people, then why not?"', '"Good,People,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m just a former saxophone player who got lucky.', '"Lucky,Who,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'There\'s enough misery in the world today without going out of the way to create more.', '"Today,World,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I walk all over Los Angeles and people seldom recognize me.', '"Walk,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Why should I knock myself out as a producer when there\'s as much money In acting - and fewer headaches.', '"Money,Myself,Acting"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m not rich but I\'ve made a little money in my time.', '"Money,Time,Rich"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I\'m sure that Steve Douglas, the character I play, has been helpful to some parents who apply his reasoning and ideas to help raise their children."', '"Character,Children,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'It was surprising for me to get out of town and have little kids ask for my autograph.', '"Me,Autograph,Town"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'You can\'t go wrong with a Western. I made a string of them.', '"Wrong,Go,Made"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'ve played a lot of cowboys.', '"Lot,Played,Cowboys"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'It\'s nice to have people tell you they leave a movie theater without any problems.', '"Problems,People,Leave"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I just don\'t want to work as hard as you have to for a TV series.', '"Work,Hard,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"They sent me the first \'Untouchables\' script, for instance, and I\'m glad I didn\'t do it. For one thing, it was practically a feature film, and for very little money. If I\'d taken it, I\'d have been faced with the job of turning them down on the series later."', '"Money,Me,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'We spend a lot of time at the ranch. And June and I spend as much time as w can with the kids. I learned with my first two how fast they grow up.', '"Time,Grow,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I don\'t want to do little theater or go on the road with a show.', '"Road,Go,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I\'m not good on talk shows.', '"Good,Talk,Talk Shows"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'You have to protect your image.', '"Image,Your,Protect"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Maybe I\'ve managed to keep my head above water through luck.', '"Water,Luck,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'A lot of actors say you can\'t do both because people won\'t pay to see you in movies when they get you for free on TV. So far it hasn\'t hurt me.', '"Movies,Me,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'Years ago my fans consisted almost strictly of adults.', '"Fans,Years Ago,Almost"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'The government has confiscated over 360 acres of my choicest pastureland to build a radar intercepting station.', '"Government,Build,Over"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I was born in Illinois, but I call Beaver Dam my home town. That\'s where I graduated from high school and started what I thought was going to be a musical career."', '"Home,School,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I remember in the movies we used to do two pages a day. One in the morning and one in the afternoon.', '"Morning,Movies,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I\'ve had offers to do series on both radio and TV, but it s so much work and I\'m lazy. I\'d rather go fishing."', '"Work,Fishing,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'You\'ve got to admire my courage going into a picture where the dog is a star. It takes a brave man to play opposite one.', '"Courage,Man,Brave"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"You know pretty well that when you\'re in a scene with a dog, everybody looks at him. I know I do."', '"Know,Dog,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"When television first came on, it had all the comedy."', '"Comedy,Television,First"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'I do enough pictures so I ran play golf and go up to my ranch once in awhile. This is what I worked towards when I began in this business in 1934.', '"Business,Enough,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', 'It\'s certain I never was meant to be an actor.', '"Never,Meant To Be,Actor"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"I can remember various stages when I wanted to be an artist, a football coach, and a musician but never an actor. However, I\'ll have to admit that now that I\'m in this business I like it and would hate to have to give it up."', '"Business,Football,Hate"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb6', '"You see, I remember myself as a tall, lanky, awkward college fellow who was cast in school theatricals, on the strength of his height alone."', '"Alone,Strength,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I always think of the character as being me. But me wearing a \'coat\', which may be a different way of speaking, moving or regarding other people. To me, acting is pretending, just like kids playing, only you pretend as if it were really, really real."', '"Character,Me,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I\'m one of relatively few stage-trained actors who doesn\'t much like acting on stage. It feels kind of like riding the Cyclone at Coney Island, which I did when I was eight. When it was all over, I was glad I had done it, but most of the time when it was actually happening, I was just kind of hanging on for dear life."', '"Life,Time,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I haven\'t appeared on stage in quite a long time and I don\'t have any immediate plans to do so, but I\'m always interested in going back."', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"Well, because I have twin seven-year-old boys, I enjoy the gift giving stuff a great deal. We do both Hanukkah and Christmas, so it is a costly, though extremely pleasing proposition."', '"Great,Christmas,Gift"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"It probably goes without saying that I enjoy the potato pancakes, delicious hams and so forth that maddeningly turn up at this time of year."', '"Time,Enjoy,Turn"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I don\'t really know of the Jewish tradition of comedy, only the Jewish tradition of not keeping your mouth shut. Complaining about all that is hard, unfair or ridiculous in life-having strong feelings, and not being able to suppress them. That, to me, is Jewish."', '"Me,Feelings,Comedy"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I have two young children with autism. What could they have ever done to deserve that? What kind of a God allows the innocent to suffer? It\'s a mystery. Yet still, I believe in God."', '"God,Believe,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"We must agree to live in this world, with all that is unfair about it, without knowing why, if we wish to have a God in our lives."', '"God,World,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"I am tolerably ignorant about Judaism, and much of what I do know about it seems hard to swallow, because it is so grounded in legalism, and adherence to rituals."', '"I Am,Know,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"Though I acted in hundreds of productions, appeared at the Guthrie Theatre and on Broadway in Amadeus, I discovered in my thirties that I didn\'t really like stage acting. The presence of the audience, the eight shows a week and the possibility of a long run were all unnatural to me."', '"Me,Long,Acting"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', '"Most of the time when I receive a script, it says something like \'Rosenberg is the fat, slovenly Mayor, who doesn\'t want the kids to use the Skateboard Park\', or \'Stein is a pompous, rotund attorney, imposing to all.\' It would be so freeing to get a script where my character is simply described as \'A Man.\'"', '"Time,Character,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb7', 'I have a secret aspiration to be considered for a part where it doesn\'t matter what you look like to play it.', '"Look,Matter,Secret"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb8', '"Tactics, fitness, stroke ability, adaptability, experience, and sportsmanship are all necessary for winning."', '"Experience,Fitness,Winning"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb8', 'I didn\'t aspire to be a good sport; \'champion\' was good enough for me.', '"Good,Me,Champion"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb8', 'McEnroe has got to sit down and work out where he stands.', '"Work,Down,Sit"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb8', '"To its great credit, Wimbledon has been a leader in bringing about change and improvement in the sport."', '"Change,Great,Improvement"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'Play is often talked about as if it were a relief from serious learning. But for children play is serious learning. Play is really the work of childhood.', '"Work,Learning,Childhood"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'The number 143 means \'I love you.\' It takes one letter to say \'I\' and four letters to say \'love\' and three letters to say \'you.\' One hundred and forty-three. \'I love you.\' Isn\'t that wonderful?', '"Love,Three,I Love You"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'Knowing that we can be loved exactly as we are gives us all the best opportunity for growing into the healthiest of people.', '"Best,Health,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"Deep and simple are far, far more important than shallow and complicated and fancy."', '"Simple,Important,Complicated"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"When I was a boy and I would see scary things in the news, my mother would say to me, \'Look for the helpers. You will always find people who are helping.\'"', '"Look,Me,News"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'How sad it is that we give up on people who are just like us.', '"Sad,People,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"The underlying message of the Neighborhood is that if somebody cares about you, it\'s possible that you\'ll care about others. \'You are special, and so is your neighbor\' - that part is essential: that you\'re not the only special person in the world. The person you happen to be with at the moment is loved, too."', '"Moment,World,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"To love someone is to strive to accept that person exactly the way he or she is, right here and now."', '"Love,Way,Accept"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"When we look for what\'s best in the person we happen to be with at the moment, we\'re doing what God does, so in appreciating our neighbor, we\'re participating in something truly sacred."', '"Best,God,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"When I was very young, most of my childhood heroes wore capes, flew through the air, or picked up buildings with one arm. They were spectacular and got a lot of attention. But as I grew, my heroes changed, so that now I can honestly say that anyone who does anything to help a child is a hero to me."', '"Hero,Childhood,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'Parents are like shuttles on a loom. They join the threads of the past with threads of the future and leave their own bright patterns as they go.', '"Future,Past,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'It\'s not the honors and not the titles and not the power that is of ultimate importance. It\'s what resides inside.', '"Power,Inside,Ultimate"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"I think everybody longs to be loved and longs to know that he or she is lovable. And, consequently, the greatest thing that we can do is to help somebody know that they\'re loved and capable of loving."', '"Help,Know,Loved"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'I think of discipline as the continual everyday process of helping a child learn self-discipline.', '"Discipline,Process,Self-Discipline"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"Love isn\'t a perfect state of caring. It\'s an active noun, like \'struggle.\'"', '"Love,Struggle,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'The space between the television set and the viewer is holy ground.', '"Space,Television,Ground"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'One of the most important gifts a parent can give a child is the gift of accepting that child\'s uniqueness.', '"Gift,Important,Uniqueness"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'All of us have special ones who have loved us into being.', '"Loved,Special,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'I do think that young children can spot a phony a mile away.', '"Children,Young,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"You know, you don\'t have to look like everybody else to be acceptable and to feel acceptable."', '"Look,Feel,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"The world is not always a kind place. That\'s something all children learn for themselves, whether we want them to or not, but it\'s something they really need our help to understand."', '"World,Children,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"Just because somebody wants to be alone sometimes, it doesn\'t mean they don\'t love you."', '"Love,Alone,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"I saw this new thing called television, and I saw people throwing pies in each other\'s faces, and I thought, \'This could be a wonderful tool for education! Why is it being used this way?\' So I said to my parents, \'You know, I don\'t think I\'ll go into seminary right away. I think I\'ll go into television.\'"', '"Education,Parents,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"I don\'t think that the basics that kids need have changed in 10,000 years."', '"Need,Think,Basics"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'Human beings need to feel that they are lovable and capable of loving.', '"Feel,Loving,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"I like to compare the holiday season with the way a child listens to a favorite story. The pleasure is in the familiar way the story begins, the anticipation of familiar turns it takes, the familiar moments of suspense, and the familiar climax and ending."', '"Way,Ending,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'The whole idea is to look at the television camera and present as much love as you possibly could to a person who might feel that he or she needs it.', '"Love,Look,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"When I first saw children\'s television, I thought it was perfectly horrible. And I thought there was some way of using this fabulous medium to be of nurture to those who would watch and listen."', '"Children,Way,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"If the day ever came when we were able to accept ourselves and our children exactly as we and they are, then, I believe, we would have come very close to an ultimate understanding of what \'good\' parenting means."', '"Good,Parenting,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', 'Children aren\'t responsible for wars.', '"Children,Responsible,Wars"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"I believe that those of us who are the producers and purveyors of television, I believe that we are the servants of this nation."', '"Believe,Television,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"The more we can be in a relationship with those who might seem strange to us, the more we can feel like we\'re neighbors and all members of the human family."', '"Family,Relationship,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feb9', '"In my own life, as the nearer I get to the end of life on this earth, the simpler I want to become."', '"Life,Earth,End"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"If people ask me for the ingredients of success, I say one is talent, two is stubbornness or determination, and third is sheer luck. You have to have two out of the three. Any two will probably do."', '"Success,Me,Determination"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"I doubt I\'ll ever do another book collaboration; I\'ve been spoiled. Roger and I both happened to move to New Mexico at about the same time, when we each had a family of young kids to raise. Socializing seemed to lead naturally to working together."', '"Family,Time,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'I have some good stories yet to tell.', '"Good,Tell,Some"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"Only towards the end of this process are any of the chapters in fully readable condition, a state of affairs that used to alarm my wife. But Joan\'s got used to it."', '"Wife,Process,End"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"And what we know, or think we know, about the universe of space and time is changing very quickly."', '"Space,Time,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"At this stage, my chief professional goal is simply to keep on writing and making a living at it."', '"Living,Professional,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"I started writing seriously about 1960, at the fairly advanced age of 30."', '"Age,Seriously,Writing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'I wouldn\'t like to just do one story or one type of stories all the time.', '"Time,Story,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"I wrote speculative fiction because I loved to read it, and thought I could do better than some of the people who were getting published."', '"Better,People,Loved"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"Mysteries I read for fun, so I will probably never write one, for fear of spoiling the fun."', '"Fear,Fun,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'Probably all the books I\'ve ever written have been efforts to define the boundaries of humanity.', '"Humanity,Boundaries,Define"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"Research is of considerable importance in certain fields, such as science and history."', '"Science,History,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"The Berserkers have been with me for about forty years, and we\'re not done yet."', '"Me,Done,Forty"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"The same tools that make any writer good, plus a cheerful willingness to suspend belief."', '"Good,Belief,Tools"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'There\'s a big overlap with the people you meet at the fantasy and science fiction cons.', '"Science,People,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'I don\'t know why a computer game can\'t be an art form just as a puppet show or an opera is. I\'m still interested in computer games as something I would like to work on someday.', '"Work,Art,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"I finally decided one day, reading science fiction magazines of the time, I could do at least as well as some of these people are doing. So I finally made a serious effort."', '"Science,Time,Effort"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'I suspect that writer\'s block afflicts mainly people who have some stable and ample source of income outside of writing. So far it hasn\'t been a problem.', '"People,Outside,Far"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"More immediately, I\'m currently working on another Dracula in which there will be connections with ancient Egypt. That\'s about as far as I want to go in commenting on current work."', '"Work,Will,Egypt"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"My gut feeling is that paper and ink are going to be with us for a long time yet, and in substantial quantities, though certainly books are now going to be available in other forms."', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"Actually ideas are everywhere. It\'s the paperwork, that is, sitting down and thinking them into a coherent story, trying to find just the right words, that can and usually does get to be labor."', '"Thinking,Words,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"I guess if one set of my books was selling like Stephen King\'s, and the other wasn\'t selling at all, editors would want me to do the ones that sold like Stephen King\'s. But they seem to be willing to let me pick what I want to do next."', '"King,Me,Next"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', 'I had immediate success in the sense that I sold something right off the bat. I thought it was going to be a piece of cake and it really wasn\'t. I have drawers full of - or I did have - drawers full of rejection slips.', '"Success,Cake,Rejection"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"The advice would be the same for any kind of fiction. Keep writing, and keep sending things out, not to friends and relatives, but to people who have the power to buy. A lot of additional, useful tips could be added, but this is fundamental."', '"Power,Advice,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"The comments I most appreciate come from ordinary readers who\'ve happened on one of my books at some time of stress in their lives, and who actually credit the book with helping them through a bad time. It\'s happened a few times in forty years."', '"Time,Bad,Stress"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"The Swords were still interesting but by then a cast of characters had started to appear and go on from book to book, and other things about the world began to feel constricting. And there were other things I wanted to do, so I closed the series up and stopped it."', '"World,Feel,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feba', '"There are interactions with characters within the game which I think are pretty neatly done considering the limitations that you have to work with. I mean, a computer can\'t really generate a character that talks back and forth with you successfully."', '"Work,Character,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Really, anyone in the business who transitions into directing as a writer or editor or an actor or a cinematographer, at some point you have to kind of take a leap and say, \'I\'m committed to this.\'"', '"Business,Leap,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'Some people look at TV as a means to an end. I look at it as my career - and one I love.', '"Love,Look,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I have been working in the entertainment industry my whole life and have always endeavored to treat everyone on any set I work on respectfully and professionally.', '"Life,Work,Treat"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I think we all have a little dark side we keep under wraps.', '"Dark,Dark Side,Side"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Ultimately, a director is a storyteller. I wanted to fortify that part of my life as a director, so I thought the best way to do that is to study and learn about the greatest stories ever written."', '"Life,Best,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Now that I\'m taking some time off from school, I\'ve been reading a lot to make sure I don\'t forget everything. It\'s mostly classics and nonfiction accounts from actors, directors and writers from the \'40s and \'50s."', '"Time,School,Forget"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I think Kellie Martin, Reese Witherspoon and Claire Danes represent the future for women in film, and I would be honored to share the stage with any one of them."', '"Future,Women,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I would suggest maintaining a life and a career outside the Industry. This is a fickle business and a lousy one to make a steady living in, so it\'s important to have a good family, friends, job and education to fall back on."', '"Life,Education,Family"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I think it is important to maintain a sense of self and confidence, not letting either falter for the sake of a particular part or project, no matter how great it might be."', '"Great,Confidence,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"As soon as it stops being fun, then I\'ll stop acting."', '"Fun,Acting,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I wasn\'t some sort of ingenue. I always saw myself as a lifer in this industry, and working as an actor on \'Wonder Years\' was a first act."', '"Myself,Always,Wonder"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Looking back at the \'Wonder Years,\' I see things I did well, and I see things I did very, very badly."', '"Looking Back,Looking,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Everything I\'ve jumped into and tried and every experience I\'ve had and career opportunity, including going to \'The Grinder,\' it was just because it sounded exciting and fun and new and different."', '"Experience,Opportunity,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Other acting opportunities had come along, but nothing that was tantalizing enough to me to step away from what I found most interesting."', '"Me,Step,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I am an English major in school with an emphasis in creative writing. I think hearing Maya Angelou speak at school last year was one of the best moments Stanford, at least, intellectually, had to offer."', '"Best,I Am,School"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I love to unwind and watch movies, especially those from the classic black-and-white era."', '"Love,Movies,Unwind"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I\'d like to see myself married with a child and hopefully still involved in the entertainment business as an actor who is also able to write a bit and direct some projects.', '"Business,Myself,Entertainment"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I\'d like to work with any actress from whom I can learn-one who has had many experiences with many directors and is willing to share some of her knowledge with me.', '"Work,Knowledge,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'It is unfortunate that the poor judgment shown by a small group of young actors has tarnished the reputation of every child who has ever appeared before a camera.', '"Poor,Young,Reputation"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"The only thing that frightens me a little is when I\'m called Kevin rather than Fred, but that\'s how people have known me for so many years. So, I can\'t really blame them."', '"Me,People,Blame"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"The term papers make me more crazy, because they involve more variables I cannot directly control! With acting, I feel more power-like I\'m making all the choices."', '"Me,Crazy,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I promised to always bring up a glass of water to her before we go to bed, and she promised to never let me dress myself."', '"Myself,Water,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'It\'s hard to sleep at night because I\'m still wondering where my mother is.', '"Night,Sleep,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I always feel bad when people ask me questions. I always felt that I was a terrible interview because I don\'t have any problems with anyone, and I don\'t have a terrible past. Or I don\'t have any terrible problems to talk about that would make interesting articles."', '"Me,Past,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"That\'s the whole reason I got into acting: I don\'t do this like some grown-ups have to do it, because they have families, and they have to make money. It\'s not my job. My dad works to support our family. So I just do it for fun."', '"Family,Money,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Whether it\'s 1970, 1990, or 2010, kids will be going through the same experiences."', '"Will,Through,Same"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Once you stop thinking about the minutiae of what each part might mean for your career, you learn that if you do a good performance, it\'s going to be good for you. The work is what matters."', '"Work,Good,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I think if you have a series for a long time, it\'s in some ways like being in a play with a long run - in that the character stays the same - and so you are constantly posed with the challenge of making it interesting and unique week after week, year after year."', '"Time,Character,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I love how restaurants work. The energy, the pace, and the idea of working under budgetary restraints reminds me a lot of sets."', '"Love,Work,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"The persona of \'The Wonder Years\' is something that\'s going to be with me forever. And I\'m happy for that. It\'s nothing that I\'d ever shy away from, and it makes me feel so good that it\'s something people still remember and talk about it and think of it so fondly."', '"Good,Me,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I think now I\'ve established myself as a director, but starting out, I\'d be foolish to think that every opportunity that came after \'The Wonder Years\' didn\'t stem from \'The Wonder Years.\' So I owe so much of everything for that show."', '"Myself,Opportunity,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'The move into adult comedy wasn\'t so much moving away from \'The Wonder Years\' as expanding myself as a director.', '"Myself,Comedy,Moving"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Directing is literally what I\'ve always wanted to do, ever since I was a kid. So I love the career I\'ve built behind the camera."', '"Love,Always,Camera"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"Going to directing wasn\'t a reaction away from acting as much as it was a move towards something I always wanted to do. Ever since I was a kid, I was interested in the camera and how it worked and why one director would place it in this part of the room and then another would place it in that part of the room."', '"Acting,Place,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I was never really aware of being famous. Being in a magazine or on a billboard - that really didn\'t register to me at all when I was younger. People would come up to me and recognize me, but I was very fortunate in that people were always so warm."', '"Famous,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I don\'t think that being an actor or being a performer at a young age leads to failures as an adult. There\'s a lot more success stories than I think people recognize.', '"Success,Age,People"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I appreciate everything. I built my career from very humble beginnings. Every job I\'ve had, every next rung on the ladder, I appreciate because I know where it started - I started doing Pac-Man vitamin commercials."', '"Humble,Know,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"I was always very interested in the storytelling decisions that went into directing. It just held this real allure for me. You know, if we\'re doing a scene at a dinner table, they weren\'t all shot the same. \'Why was the camera here for one moment and there for another?\'"', '"Moment,Me,Dinner"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', 'I don\'t really spend a lot of time discounting the things I\'m doing in hopes that I could be doing something else.', '"Time,Doing,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febb', '"You can still have a very productive, crime-free life when you\'re growing up in show business."', '"Life,Business,Growing Up"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"No, we\'ve been performing our old songs a little differently each performance."', '"Old Songs,Performance,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'It was a nightmare. The band had to tour Greenland by bus.', '"Band,Bus,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"I never planned on a career in music at all, so I should say I\'m very lucky."', '"Music,Never,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"Everything changed after \'Love Shack.\' We went \'mainstream.\' \'Love Shack\' set what people viewed us as, because a lot of people didn\'t realize we had a career before that."', '"Love,People,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'The hairstyles of most Heavy Metal bands are pretty horrendous.', '"Heavy Metal,Metal,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'A good fruit cake is good fruit cake. A bad one is really bad.', '"Good,Fruit,Cake"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"We don\'t have a constant PR person or anything. That\'s why people say. \'Oh, you\'re still together?\' Yeah. I\'m in Des Moines with the band, not because I\'m sightseeing."', '"Together,People,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"It doesn\'t cost me anything to write some fun stuff for folks, because I just really enjoy a challenge."', '"Me,Fun,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I was raised in New Jersey - Long Branch.', '"Long,New,New Jersey"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I used to like doing karaoke until cell-phone cameras came along.', '"Doing,Like,Along"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'Australians are geniuses with a good sense of humour.', '"Good,Humour,Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'Call us the future from your past.', '"Future,Past,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I am a pacifist.', '"I Am,Am,Pacifist"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I rarely watch TV but I guess I\'d watch the weather report since I fly so much.', '"Weather,Fly,Guess"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'Sometimes groups and their material can get overbloated.', '"Sometimes,Get,Material"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"You know, Southerners are pretty cool."', '"Cool,Know,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"I was interested in wildlife conservation, and I chose Georgia because they supposedly had a good forestry school. I figured it might be easier to get good grades there, too, because a lot of Southern kids would come up to school in New Jersey, and they\'d always be a little behind, so I figured maybe I wouldn\'t have to work so hard."', '"Work,Good,New"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'There are a lot of people who are considered \'camp\' who have no idea how ridiculous they are.', '"People,Ridiculous,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"\'Camp\' sort of means you don\'t know what you\'re doing, and we know what we\'re doing."', '"Know,Doing,Means"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'We\'ve never tried to fit any mould because we already broke the one we started.', '"Never,Because,Tried"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"We\'ve always shared everything - writing credits, all the royalties - and there\'s no real leader because if there was one, we\'d immediately depose them."', '"Real,Always,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I like Loretta Lynn.', '"Like,Lynn"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"There are a lot of funny motels. There was one motel in the middle of nowhere: it was real plain, but it had a gigantic green monster, something like the Creature from the Black Lagoon, standing next to this lake."', '"Funny,Black,Green"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'We are lucky to have a big fan base and that we can support ourselves doing live shows.', '"Support,Live,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:07:00', '2023-05-29 12:07:00'),
	('401266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"Our look evolved from the fact that we bought thrift-store clothes. It wasn\'t like, \'Let adopt a thrift-store aesthetic.\' We just didn\'t have any money."', '"Money,Look,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I feel like I have a distinct voice.', '"Feel,Voice,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"People think that I live in a space pod, but it\'s pretty mid-century modern."', '"Space,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I collect all kinds of things.', '"Things,Kinds,Collect"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"I always wear Chuck Taylors, but then I found out that you could actually get your own shoes, so I mentioned it to the band, and they said, \'Yeah! Let\'s do it\' And we got \'em. That\'s how it works."', '"Shoes,Always,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"Back in the day, when we\'d get into a town, I would go in the phone book and look up record stores. Then I\'d take a bus or a cab and check them out."', '"Look,Day,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"We weren\'t art students, but we definitely created our own style and were pretty influenced by Andy Warhol and all the stuff we read and saw and made fun of, you know."', '"Art,Style,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I like Scissor Sisters.', '"Like,Sisters"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"Jim Hightower, Ann Richards - there are quite a few intelligent regular Texans."', '"Intelligent,Quite,Few"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I was the meal delivery coordinator for Clarke County for Meals on Wheels.', '"Delivery,Meal,Wheels"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', '"I am so not hooked into watching TV or listening to the radio, to be honest. Usually, when I do, I get angry."', '"Angry,I Am,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febc', 'I\'ll tell you what: Everything about the Trump administration is scary.', '"Everything,Tell,Administration"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', 'Everything about \'Adventure Time\' is the purest form of kid\'s play. A kid does not live in the Land of Ooo. That is one of the wonderful things about the show; it doesn\'t pretend to be real. That was the great thing about \'Pee Wee\'s Playhouse\'; it existed in a world completely outside any reality a kid recognized.', '"Time,Great,Reality"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', 'Cartoon Hangover has given us another place we felt we could find the most talented people around the world and give them a chance to make the films they want to make and match it up with their audience.', '"Chance,World,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"One of the most effective ways we started our web efforts in the early 2000s with our first channel Frederator, we basically showcased 1000\'s of shows on our show over a few years and what that did was introduce us to talented people from all across the world, you name it, we met people all over the place."', '"World,People,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', 'I tell people if I want to make a film I just go make it so you can make yours.', '"People,Go,Tell"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"I come from a time when pop music was the coin of the cultural realm and in a certain way was the only coin of the realm; movies didn\'t matter as much, and not TV - it was all about pop music. In the era when I started - which was the early \'60s - it was all about singles leading to albums."', '"Time,Music,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"If you were to look at an old \'Betty Boop\' cartoon or an \'Out of the Ink Well\' animation, there are many things about \'Adventure Time\' that really remind you of that, even though it doesn\'t look like any of those cartoons."', '"Time,Look,Cartoons"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"I really like dating stories, like in Betty and Veronica comics; I like David Lynch and H.P. Lovecraft for the dark gut-wrenching stuff, and I\'m inspired by Miyazaki\'s films for the subtle heart-warming moments, as well as the moments that blew up my imagination."', '"Dating,Imagination,Dark"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"The early seasons of \'The Simpsons\' had a great deal of heart. That\'s what I\'m trying to pull from, the kind of stuff that goes straight to kids\' hearts. When they\'re watching, they don\'t necessarily know why they love something."', '"Love,Great,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"Up until the time Turner Broadcasting bought Hanna-Barbera, it was essentially an independent studio whose planning cycle had to be nine months. You got a pickup in January, and you put it on the air in September. That\'s been the cycle."', '"Time,Independent,Planning"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"If you mentioned Hanna-Barbera to people, they said, \'Oh yeah, Flintstone, Yogi, Scooby-Doo, Jetsons,\' and that was pretty much it. We have characters with very high recognition factors and great films, but no organized plans for really making the most of them and increasing their value."', '"Great,Value,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"My background is that I\'ve spent a lot of time marketing entertainment. One of the old saws in package goods is you can take something that is popular and you can make it more popular. But if you take something less popular, you can\'t automatically market it into the same success as something that\'s already popular."', '"Success,Time,Entertainment"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febd', '"Castle Rock and New Line each have their strengths, but the great thing about New Line is that they are a real focused-market, niche-market player who understand franchises. They probably understand the franchise business in motion pictures better than anyone else out there."', '"Business,Great,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"I didn\'t even think demographics until I got to ABC. They were the first to go for 18-to-49. But, at CBS, it was just, \'Let\'s get \'em in the tent.\'"', '"Go,First,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"The first sales meeting I made was for the television movie \'Farrell for the People.\' I walked into a conference room at NBC that I had built. It was my memorial conference room. There were 10 people at the meeting, and by habit, I sat at the head of the table."', '"Habit,People,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"You find a personality whom you think the TV audience will embrace and find a format that is tailor-made for the personality. In the case of Andy Griffith, we moved the personality of a wily country shark - a funny and shrewd guy - into another arena. In this case, he is a lawyer, and it is a dramatic series."', '"Funny,Personality,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', 'The kind of audience that watches \'Matlock\' is ideal for a lead-in to the affiliates\' newscast in the afternoon. That audience is older.', '"Afternoon,Watches,Audience"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', 'The only way to stop the erosion in network television is to come up with shows that are very popular.', '"Way,Television,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"You acquire certain tastes. And if your taste happens to coincide with the majority of people, then you\'re in pretty good shape. But you\'re not always right. There were times when I stubbed my toe, and some will end up being on my tombstone - like \'Supertrain.\'"', '"Good,People,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"I was the King of Twinkie-Vision one day, the King of Jiggle TV the next, thanks to Farrah Fawcett and \'Three\'s Company.\'"', '"King,Day,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"Funny is funny, whether you have three cameras or one."', '"Funny,Three,Whether"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"There seems to be a vulnerability at the networks in late night. They are losing more and more audience, particularly young viewers who are now looking at cable television. \'Tonight\' is an old show. CBS has reruns, and having a public affairs series like \'Nightline\' on ABC is a big mistake."', '"Night,Mistake,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febe', '"Succeeding in network prime time has gotten tougher. Every day, several thousand homes are wired for cable, and more people are buying videodisks and video cassettes. That all represents competition."', '"Time,Competition,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"That is, while we believe that cost-benefit analysis is an important tool to inform agency decision making, the results of the cost-benefit analysis do not trump existing law."', '"Decision,Believe,Law"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"And when we draw lines in the sand with regard to certain basic things that are vital to our interest and to the interest of democracy and our friends around the world, we have to be willing to back that up."', '"Democracy,World,Sand"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'There\'s a lot more to competence than a law degree and a modicum of courtroom skill.', '"Skill,Law,Degree"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"Some people think that our planet is suffering from a fever. Now scientists are telling us that Mars is experiencing its own planetary warming: Martian warming. This has led some people, not necessarily scientists, to wonder if Mars and Jupiter, non signatories to the Kyoto Treaty, are actually inhabited by alien SUV-driving industrialists."', '"Suffering,People,Alien"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"While we believe there are fruitful opportunities to update and improve old rules, we do not want to set up a review process that could create a litigation morass."', '"Believe,Process,Rules"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'Nobody wants to open a business near a Superfund site and risk being sued.', '"Business,Nobody,Open"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"Let\'s not overlook, though, what we do know about the campaign finance scandal, and the fact the Chinese were involved in our presidential campaign and our congressional campaigns."', '"Finance,Know,Campaign"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"In the end, we may be hurting the very people we should be concerned about - the inner-city poor, those who already have to live with many risks in their daily lives, those who do not have clout here in Washington."', '"Daily,Risks,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"For a long time in American history, people didn\'t even come up before the Senate. They didn\'t come before the Judiciary Committee, and up until about 1923, something like that."', '"History,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"We have some real political differences among us, but we all share the same goals: clean air and water, injury free workplaces, safe transportation systems, to name a few of the good things that can come from regulation."', '"Good,Water,Political"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"But if the Chinese mainland, the PRC, attacked Taiwan, we\'d be obligated to come to their aid."', '"Come,Taiwan,Chinese"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"So China will be having to make some choices as to whose side it wants to be on. Hopefully, this will be the beginning of a major improvement in our relationship with them, if they choose correctly."', '"Relationship,Improvement,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"But obviously, we can\'t afford to make some bad long-term decisions with regard to basic commitments our country has - trade those away for some short-term assistance that may or may not be there a month from now."', '"Bad,Country,Long-Term"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"We\'re hoping for the best, but we need to prepare for the worst."', '"Best,Worst,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"And I believe in the 13 years Judge Roberts was there, he never turned down a request to give some assistance on a pro-bono case, and this was no different."', '"Believe,Never,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'And it\'s difficult for the average American to understand why something like that could be so important and why a little small place like Taiwan would be so important to the PRC.', '"Difficult,Important,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'China is one of the world\'s greatest proliferators of weapons of mass destruction to these rogue nations.', '"World,China,Destruction"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"Clearly, the Chinese know that we want a good relationship with them."', '"Relationship,Good,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"For example, lead paint in old houses can be a greater threat to children\'s health than lead that may be under some industrial site where there are no children."', '"Health,Children,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"Hopefully, we can build bridges, but we also have to draw lines."', '"Build,Lines,Bridges"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"I think that the justices were totally answering the way that they should. I think that the senators, as best I could tell, for the most part, Democrat and Republican, respected that."', '"Best,Way,Republican"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'I think that there is a relatively small number of people who are pushing for independence in Taiwan.', '"Independence,People,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"So if you look back over the long history of China, they\'ve never tried to take over the world, but they\'ve been quite aggressive in their own neighborhood... in carrying out their own purposes and interests in their sphere of the world."', '"History,Look,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"Sometimes you have to, as I say, build bridges where you can - but draw lines where you must."', '"Sometimes,Build,Lines"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'Superfund was passed with the good intention of cleaning up America\'s toxic waste sites.', '"Good,America,Cleaning"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'The problem is that agencies sometimes lose sight of common sense as they create regulations.', '"Lose,Sometimes,Common Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'We also have to ask if we focusing on the most important priorities.', '"Important,Priorities,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"We just ask the agency to make reasonable and honest decisions, and the public deserves no less."', '"Decisions,Just,Reasonable"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', '"We\'ve made some mistakes in this country in times past - the Korean conflict proceeding that, some say proceeding the Persian Gulf War, where we were ambiguous as to what we would do."', '"War,Past,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24febf', 'You can\'t substitute promise after promise with known violators of prior promises at the expense of protecting ourselves or setting an example.', '"Promises,Example,Substitute"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"The small amount of people that control the discourse around painting - I thought that the whole museum world was just a bunch of phonies, and I didn\'t really want to have anything to do with it. I guess I did installations, in a funny way, because they couldn\'t be commodified."', '"Funny,World,Painting"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"I like the idea of multidisciplinary conversations, so in that spirit, I try and make a contribution from the art world into the music world."', '"Art,Music,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"There are aspects of Asian culture in my work, but it\'s really rooted in an American experience - transcendentalism, \'60s counterculture, punk rock."', '"Work,Experience,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', 'I wouldn\'t know any other way to live except to be an artist. I\'m not very good at anything else.', '"Good,Way,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"Art is really about perception, and mine have been changed through visiting other realities."', '"Art,Perception,Mine"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', 'I\'m actually pretty smart when you get to know me.', '"Me,Smart,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"I don\'t embrace irony, but I do think it\'s a pre-existing condition; we manage it as best we can."', '"Best,Irony,Embrace"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', 'I kind of have a Victorian sensibility - I don\'t understand stuff until I can classify it and name it.', '"Name,I Can,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"I worked my way through art school as an auto mechanic, doing various stuff including sanding bodywork and using Bondo filler."', '"Art,Way,School"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"I\'ve come to believe in the primacy of form - the notion of art seducing you through your senses, through your eyeballs."', '"Art,Believe,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"I don\'t know if I\'m a populist artist, but I do try to maintain a spirit of generosity."', '"Spirit,Know,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec0', '"A lot of people don\'t think of my work as being all that funny, but I think it\'s hilarious!"', '"Funny,Work,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'New discoveries and production of resources like shale oil and gas are dramatically altering our energy supply outlook and the entire global geopolitical landscape. And the pace of change - particularly in the past few years - continues to accelerate.', '"Change,Energy,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"You shouldn\'t have an overbearing FCC. Let the market work itself. By allowing companies to compete in an unregulated forum, you\'re going to allow the faster deployment of new services and new equipment consumers are going to want."', '"Work,New,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Our work on light bulbs wasn\'t an arbitrary mandate. We didn\'t just pick a standard out of the air, or look for a catchy sounding standard like 25 by 2025 not based in science or feasibility. Instead, we worked with both industry and environmental groups to come up with a standard that made sense and was doable."', '"Work,Science,Environmental"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'I support renewable energy.', '"Energy,Support,Renewable Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Together, we will protect the sanctity of life, ensuring early next Congress that no federal funds are used for abortion."', '"Life,Together,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"I support an all of the above energy policy, so that\'s not only just Keystone, that\'s not only just drilling, that\'s clean coal, that\'s safe nuclear."', '"Energy,Support,Safe"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Americans want and deserve a broad array of health insurance choices so they can identify those that best fit their own individual or family needs. These choices expand when we allow free enterprise to foster innovation, not smother it with taxes and one-size fits all ideology."', '"Best,Family,Health"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Without international participation, jobs and emissions will simply shift overseas to countries that require few, if any, environmental protections, harming the global environment as well as the U.S. economy."', '"Environmental,Will,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"People in Michigan are good at separating fact from fiction. They know, better than most of the country, what happens to the economy and jobs when the scales are tipped too far in favor of one group over another."', '"Good,Better,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'The Obama administration is on notice - they will not be allowed to regulate what they have been unable to legislate.', '"Will,Administration,Notice"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"For those broadcasters who are less than responsible, the FCC needs to have sharper teeth to enforce the law."', '"Law,Teeth,Needs"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"While the Left seems obsessed with increasing taxes and spending even more money, conservatives have focused more heavily on the need for spending restraint and entitlement reform - primarily to preserve and protect the future of the Medicare program. Overlooked in all of this is the future of Medicaid."', '"Future,Money,More"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"If the EPA continues unabated, jobs will be shipped to China and India as energy costs skyrocket. Most of the media attention has focused on the EPA\'s efforts to regulate climate-change emissions, but that is just the beginning."', '"Energy,Media,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Originally created to serve the poorest and sickest among us, the Medicaid program has grown dramatically but still doesn\'t include the kind of flexibility that states need to provide better health care for the poor and disadvantaged."', '"Health,Care,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"It\'s critical - that the people that are benefiting today from Medicare and Social Security that they not see benefit reductions. It\'s awfully hard to tell someone who might be 82, that they\'ve gotta go back to work, because their benefits are gonna be chopped. That\'s not gonna happen."', '"Work,Today,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'Obamacare represents a shocking display of political arrogance. It\'s about time Washington started listening to Americans\' common sense voices.', '"Time,Political,Arrogance"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'Common sense tells us that this explosion of media sources should eliminate any concern over a lack of diversity of views in the marketplace and competition.', '"Competition,Diversity,Media"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"We\'ve heard this before; \'things are bad, we are gonna fix them,\' and they remain unfixed."', '"Bad,Things,Fix"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"I think we can lower our emissions. I think the world will be better off if we did that, and we can do it without cap and trade."', '"World,Better,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"I look forward to standing shoulder to shoulder with Speaker Boehner, Leader Cantor, Whip McCarthy and the entire republican conference as we repeal Obamacare, fight rampant job killing regulations, cut spending and help put folks back to work."', '"Work,Fight,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'Cuts in carbon emissions would mean significantly higher electricity prices. We think the American consumer would prefer not to be skinned by Obama\'s EPA.', '"American,Electricity,Mean"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"I\'m a Reagan Republican, which means I don\'t speak ill of other Republicans."', '"Speak,Republican,Means"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'I know the exploding cost of health care is at the root of our long-term fiscal challenges.', '"Health,Challenges,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'We cannot afford the EPA\'s continued expansion of red tape that is slowing economic growth and threatening to entangle millions of small businesses.', '"Growth,Red,Economic Growth"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"I\'m not a rubber stamp, and people know that. If you can convince me of the merits, you will have my vote every time."', '"Time,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Nuclear is not only emissions-free, but renewing our commitment to nuclear power will create countless jobs at a time when our nation endures nearly double-digit unemployment."', '"Time,Power,Commitment"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Prior to passage of Obamacare, Americans spoke out against the individual mandate; they didn\'t want to change the health care they had; they didn\'t want a 3,000-page bill that empowered 15 Washington bureaucrats to decide the future of the doctor-patient relationship."', '"Change,Health,Future"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Under President Obama\'s new health care law, Medicaid will become a very different health coverage program than first envisioned."', '"Health,Law,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"The national debate on health care once centered on improving access to quality care, yet the effect of Obamacare will be the exact opposite, resulting in the shameful degradation of care for the neediest individuals."', '"Health,Quality,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', 'An imposing wall prominently divides the visions of President Obama and congressional Republicans when it comes to economic growth and creating jobs. Solyndra is on one side and the Keystone pipeline is on the other.', '"Growth,Economic Growth,Creating"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"With the discovery of vast new North American energy resources - thanks to the application of proven technologies like hydraulic fracturing and commonsense regulatory processes on non-federal lands - the U.S. government should no longer be in the business of spending taxpayer dollars on risky, exotic energy projects."', '"Business,Government,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Given the slow pace of Washington\'s bureaucracy, policymakers are often busy solving yesterday\'s problems. This rearview mirror approach afflicts Mr. Obama and his Democratic allies in Congress."', '"Mirror,Busy,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Obamacare is a seriously flawed law that makes health care coverage less affordable, costs taxpayers more than advertised and fails to deliver on most of its other grand promises."', '"Health,Law,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec1', '"Giving governors more leeway in administering health care could represent a small, positive development in the ongoing saga of Obamacare. Unfortunately, instead of choosing flexibility, President Obama and his left-leaning advisers always default to rigid \'Washington knows best\' answers."', '"Positive,Best,Health"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec2', 'TV is bigger than any story it reports. It\'s the greatest teaching tool since the printing press.', '"Teacher,Printing,Story"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec2', 'A composite is a euphemism for a lie. It\'s disorderly. It\'s dishonest and it\'s not journalism.', '"Journalism,Lie,Dishonest"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec2', '"Television was supposed to be a national park. Instead it has become a money machine. It\'s a commodity now, just like pork bellies."', '"Money,Television,Park"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec2', 'Television makes so much at its worst that it can\'t afford to do its best.', '"Best,Worst,Television"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec2', '"The news is the one thing the networks can point to with pride. Everything else they do is crap, and they know it."', '"Pride,News,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"I think we\'re struggling with trying to redefine various positions at this point in history. To allow freedom for women, freedom for men, freedom from those sharply defined gender roles."', '"Freedom,History,Women"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"If some woman tells me how she feels about something, my immediate assumption is that she wants an answer, or that she wants me to solve her problem. In fact, all she wants to do is share, or show how she feels."', '"Me,Woman,Answer"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', 'I doing casual labor by the day. They wouldn\'t pay you until the next morning. There was a bar that would cash your check if you bought a beer first. A lot of guys never left until they\'d drunk up all their money.', '"Money,Morning,Drunk"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', 'Trying different things is very important to me. I see people and want to wear their clothes and drive in their cars for awhile. That\'s probably one reason I became an actor.', '"Me,Drive,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"As an actor, it\'s fun to play guys who aren\'t just locked into a male pattern, but a lot of guys you\'re asked to play are fairly macho and have a certain rigid standard they\'re living by."', '"Fun,Living,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"I was just talking about women, just in terms of understanding them as much as we can ever understand the opposite sex. I\'m trying to let go of certain male approaches to things that you inherit, that you grow up with."', '"Women,Sex,Grow"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', 'In the beginning Remo is a very New York street cop who changes and is changed as he moves along.', '"Street,Beginning,New"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', 'There was always a creative impulse in me but I never felt rooted to anything.', '"Me,Never,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"In this play we\'re dealing with relative truths - who\'s lying, who\'s telling the truth. But underneath that, Ed and I have hit this deeper level of intimacy between old friends that comes out in the play."', '"Truth,Old Friends,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"I like to spread myself out. Since I was a kid, I always recognized some void."', '"Myself,Always,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"It\'s a major part of world history that men are trying to kill each other. It\'s just one slaughter after the other. We talk about it, but no one\'s really listening."', '"History,Men,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"It\'s like a prehistoric reflex, you know, going out and getting the meat and bringing it back to the cave. You feel you\'re supposed to make it better, but more than likely she\'s asking you to tell her how you feel."', '"Better,Feel,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', 'My career has been a bit strange. I don\'t think it took the normal route.', '"Strange,Normal,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec3', '"When you\'re a father, you know exactly where your heart really is. There\'s no question of it, no doubt. That part of your life has no second guessing."', '"Life,Heart,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I\'ve found over the years that for some reason, people either are big fans and have to use me, or they don\'t quite understand what I\'m doing."', '"Me,People,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I still think \'Texas Chain Saw Massacre\' was what they call one of those watershed movies. That and \'The Exorcist\' and \'Psycho\' were just landmarks for those horror films.', '"Movies,Psycho,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I\'ve always wanted to be on a soap opera.', '"Always,Opera,Soap"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"As an actor, and as you get to a certain level... and it\'s pilot season and you read the trades, you could have a nervous breakdown. \'So-and-so\'s signed for a pilot. Why aren\'t I?\'"', '"Why,Nervous,Pilot"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"One of the first shows I ever did was \'Laverne & Shirley.\' I played this sleazy guy that came into town with a friend and was going to date Laverne and Shirley, but we really wanted to get into the bowling alley because it was next to the bank we wanted to rob."', '"Bank,Next,Friend"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I guess it\'s from going to Virginia Military Institute. I\'m a good person to follow orders.', '"Good,Good Person,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"When we need a policeman, God bless \'em, they\'re there. But, if you\'re in the wrong place at the wrong time, everything seems suspicious."', '"God,Time,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I just look back, and I say, you know, Christopher Guest just raised my whole career to another level."', '"Look,Back,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I don\'t know why my lines that were cut from the film didn\'t make it onto the DVD. I have offered to go into the editing room with Christopher and work shoulder to shoulder with him to fit all my lines in. I think he thinks I\'m kidding. I\'m only trying to help.', '"Work,Editing,Help"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'People still quote my lines from \'Best in Show.\'', '"Best,People,Lines"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Some of the Christopher Guest movies, when I\'m not really like myself, when I have my hair dyed blonde or had a faux-hawk haircut. Those I like to watch because it takes you away from your real self."', '"Movies,Myself,Haircut"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I really enjoy working on \'Modern Family.\'', '"Family,Enjoy,Modern"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Bob Balaban is so perfect that the first movie I did with him, I couldn\'t talk to him because I was so intimidated by him."', '"Perfect,Talk,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"With improv or a full length play - you know how you go to a theater, and after 10 minutes you say, \'Oh, I don\'t like this thing,\' but you don\'t want to get up and leave? At a sketch show, it\'s always something new every few minutes."', '"New,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I try to shy away from playing cranky people, but if it\'s just a funny next-door neighbor or business man, I\'ll say, \'Sure, why not?\'"', '"Funny,Business,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I\'ll go in a minute to see a sketch show.', '"See,Go,Minute"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I think everyone has a door in their brain that says, \'Do not exit here.\' If you go past it, you\'ll find all the dumb thoughts in there, all the stupid things that shouldn\'t be said. I\'ve probably gone there more than anyone should in a given lifetime."', '"Stupid,Thoughts,Brain"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I think if you have a funny thought, and you want to get off a funny point, try to do it as realistically as you can. If you try to act it funny and accent the funny points, or do it in a funny style, you kind of lose it."', '"Funny,Lose,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I did a show called \'Lois & Clark\' - it was about Superman - years ago. They wanted someone to play the president of the United States. The plot was the president got kidnapped by a group, and they made a clone of him, who was very irresponsible and silly."', '"Group,Someone,Irresponsible"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I always loved comedy growing up - Bob Hope, Red Skelton and Danny Kaye."', '"Hope,Comedy,Red"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I first became interested in \'great moments\' when I read about the famous Feller-to-Boudreau pickoff play in the 1948 World series.', '"Great,Famous,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"In most cities, it doesn\'t cost much to put your own show on a local access channel, so you get all sorts of strange stuff on the air."', '"Air,Own,Strange"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I like to play the guy that has no self-awareness.', '"Self-Awareness,Play,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"It\'s such a pleasure to work in these movies, it\'s almost like it\'s not really happening."', '"Work,Movies,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Let me say this: I have said, any time, if it\'s Martin Mull, I will say yes. If it\'s Christopher Guest, I will say yes."', '"Time,Me,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I just love everything that Disney and Pixar do. Not only do they do beautiful films, but they have great messages for kids."', '"Love,Great,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I think my wife saw a picture of the rock group Journey, and they\'re kind of aging, and the one guy had dyed blonde hair with black roots, and... my idea was to get a little earring, I wanted to have a dangling earring."', '"Journey,Black,Wife"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Suddenly you\'re like a pirate, you\'re 65 years old and you\'ve got an earring."', '"Old,Like,Pirate"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"It\'s more fun in a way to do ensemble scenes, where you know your background, you know the scene, but you can\'t prepare because someone else is going to say something that is going to lead you off."', '"Fun,Way,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Someone I\'ve always admired is Catherine O\'Hara... I think she\'s one of the best actresses in the country, not only comedy. I just think she\'s just a step aside from everybody, she\'s just wonderful."', '"Best,Step,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I just admire everybody and sit in awe and watch them.', '"Admire,Sit,Watch"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Cleveland is my hometown, and the Indians have a narrow but rich history."', '"History,Hometown,Rich"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I once was in a project. They were going to do a remake. Somebody started a rumor I wanted more money. I said, \'This is ridiculous. I\'d kill for this project!\'"', '"Money,Project,More"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I never think I\'m old enough to play someone\'s dad, even though I have a daughter of my own and a grandson."', '"Dad,Never,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'God bless Chris Guest... and I mean it sincerely.', '"God,Mean,God Bless"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"My first improv was Second City in Chicago. Before that, I worked at - with a partner, doing comedy sketches."', '"City,Comedy,Partner"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"It scared me to death to think about improv, but I got hired for a year at Second City in Chicago, which made me nervous, but I found I could improvise. Then I was in a group called the Ace Trucking Company, which we\'d do, like, a half hour set of material, then open up for improvisation."', '"Death,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"There\'s different kinds of improv. There\'s Second City improv where you try to slowly build a nice sketch. There\'s stuff you do in college coffee houses where you just go joke, joke, joke. Bring another funny character with a funny hat on his head. Christopher Guest is more the line of trying to get a story out."', '"Funny,Character,City"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'The \'Tim And Eric\' experience was very strange.', '"Experience,Strange,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Christopher Guest, he\'ll call and say, \'We\'re doing this movie, and I\'d like you to play _\' and he gives you the character, then I always like to enlarge on the character."', '"Character,Doing,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"That\'s always a funny thing, when people think they\'re known for every little thing they ever did, and they\'re really not."', '"Funny,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Tobe Hooper - he did my favorite horror movie, \'Texas Chain Saw Massacre.\' It\'s still one of my favorite horror films."', '"He,Horror,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"If I have to play an obnoxious character, try to find a redeeming feature of him. The most obnoxious people in the world were people, and they had had a reason for doing what they did. So you try to find that and let the obnoxiousness come out."', '"Character,World,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I never got any advice in acting.', '"Advice,Acting,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"If you\'re a cheerleader, people see you. If you\'re a mascot, you\'re just helping out."', '"People,See,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I guess if you\'re a professional mascot, you\'re doing it for the money, but a college mascot just wants to be out there."', '"Money,Doing,Professional"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"When you think about accountants, who would want to be an accountant? But, what would we do without accountants? Whether it\'s soldiers or garbage men or doctors, everyone has the thing that they love."', '"Love,Men,Accountant"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"All America is familiar with the Yankee-Dodger-Giant trivia, but so many other teams had great moments."', '"Great,America,Moments"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I love sketch; it\'s my favorite form. But if it\'s all improv, they\'re either very good, and it\'s annoying how good they are, and it makes you feel bad, or they\'re not too good; then you\'re sweating for them."', '"Love,Good,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'It\'s not a bad typecast: the goofy guy.', '"Bad,Goofy,Guy"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I had just done a movie called \'How to Beat the High Cost of Living,\' and it didn\'t get a good review. And the same people sent me the script for \'Airplane!\' for the Robert Hays part. I read it, and there were a lot of plays on words, and I said, \'I don\'t like this kind of comedy.\'"', '"Good,Me,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I\'ve been in a lot of shows, I will say that. Every once in a while, I\'ll look at a tape of something I\'ve done, and I won\'t even remember having done it."', '"Look,Remember,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'Getting those parts in the Christopher Guest movies was the second biggest helper to my career after \'Fernwood.\'', '"Movies,Second,After"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"When I started, there was a phase where I wanted to be a cowboy star. I didn\'t want to do deep, serious parts."', '"Serious,Want,Deep"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I loved Bob Hope and the way he would turn to the camera and break the fourth wall.', '"Hope,Way,Camera"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'Comedy always came easier for me. But I would have loved to have been an action hero.', '"Hero,Me,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"If you\'re going to take a risk as a comic, make sure it\'s surrounded by other things that you\'re certain are funny."', '"Funny,Surrounded,Comic"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Comedy relieves you. A lot of times, we think we\'re the only people bothered by certain things. Then you hear a comic say, \'Don\'t you hate it when...\' And it\'s, \'Oh, my God! Of course!\'"', '"God,Hate,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'A great director is someone who makes you feel like you\'re moving forward.', '"Great,Feel,Moving Forward"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'One of the great things about kids is they haven\'t heard a lot of the old jokes. You can get away with the corny ones.', '"Great,Great Things,Old"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I love to draw, although I wish I was better at it."', '"Love,Better,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I have great respect for the authorities.', '"Respect,Great,Authorities"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Everybody I run into goes, \'Hey, \'Best in Show!\'\' Or, \'Hey, that dog movie!\' which I don\'t mind because I\'m not too good on titles."', '"Best,Good,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'There\'s this whole underground world of amateur television production.', '"World,Television,Underground"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'How can we say any one actor\'s work was better than another\'s?', '"Work,Better,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'Martin Landau in \'Crimes and Misdemeanors\' - he gave me chills.', '"Me,He,Chills"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"If I like a movie, I see no reason not to go back for Parts 2, 3, 4, etc."', '"Back,See,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"\'Field of Dreams.\' Definitely one of the best baseball films of all time. When Kevin Costner spoke to his dad, and his dad answered, I, um, I mean a lot of guys I know couldn\'t help crying."', '"Dreams,Best,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '\'Fernwood 2-Night\' didn\'t help me too much when it was first on.', '"Me,Help,Too Much"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I\'ve never crossed over to be a big star. I\'d like to be in a big $100 million movie, though. \'Cause I was in an \'Austin Powers,\' I think I had two lines, and every once in a while, I get a check, a really nice check, for that movie."', '"Never,Big,Nice"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I have a guy who does my hair. He\'s a car nut. And he was taking motorcycle lessons. And, what was my point?"', '"Car,Hair,Motorcycle"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Comedy is harder, because if there\'s no laughs, it\'s pretty bad. But drama, if there\'s no reaction, you can say, \'Well, it\'s not their cup of tea. Maybe it\'s too heavy for the audience.\'"', '"Drama,Bad,Tea"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Looking back, I was a very good kid, very studious and all. But I would always come out with a quip - and I was sent to the principal\'s office several times."', '"Good,Looking Back,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"If you\'re not doing something right, you can feel it on stage, and if it isn\'t going well, the audience will tell you. A teacher can teach you sense memory and this and that, but until you get in front of an audience, you don\'t really feel it."', '"Teacher,Memory,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I have always been more relaxed around comedy.', '"Comedy,Always,More"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I used to collect autographs outside of the old Cleveland Stadium. I can still remember everyone who took the time and spent a few minutes to make your day. That sticks with you.', '"Time,Day,Remember"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I\'ll talk your ear off if you recognize me.', '"Me,Talk,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"After working with Wayne Brady, Colin Mochrie, and Jonathan Mangum, I said, \'I am never going to talk about improv again.\'"', '"I Am,Never,Talk"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Because I started my career in improv, performing with Second City and the Ace Trucking Company, I always enjoy being in situations where - as an actor - you have to think fast & be light on your feet."', '"Light,City,Feet"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I love working with Ty Burrell.', '"Love,Working,I Love"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"My father passed away when I was 12, so it was very difficult. But I was always the class clown. I don\'t know why - maybe as an escape. But then I was sent away to military prep school."', '"Father,Difficult,Escape"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"My stepfather was a military man: he was in the Air Force. Reserve. You thought he\'d seen front-line action, but he was stationed in Cleveland."', '"Man,Action,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I was an only child.', '"Child,Only,Only Child"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I\'d love to have Burt Reynolds\' career.', '"Love,Career"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I love San Francisco!', '"Love,I Love,San Francisco"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I guess the essence of my comedy is to get into a very abnormal situation but act like it\'s normal.', '"Situation,Comedy,Act"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I am re-collecting the baseball cards my mom had thrown out when I went away to school. You know you are an adult when you can buy a whole set of baseball cards instead of two packs at a time.', '"Time,Mom,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"To a New Yorker, a 1948 Indians World Series baseball signed by the whole team might be worth only $200 to $300, but to a Clevelander like myself, it might be, like, $1,000 to $2,000."', '"Myself,World,New"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'I like the characters that have some redeeming quality or if it\'s interesting to me in any way.', '"Me,Quality,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', 'The witch in \'Snow White\' is a very scary image.', '"White,Image,Scary"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"I saw the \'Wizard of Oz\' recently and realized that, all my life, I thought they were real monkeys with wings. That\'s how scary that movie was for me."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec4', '"Kids can relate to having some scary person living near their house. They can relate to, \'Hey, don\'t go near that house.\' We all can."', '"Living,Person,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"I\'m really interested in the intersection between reputation, identity, and knowledge."', '"Knowledge,Identity,Reputation"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Venture capital is about capturing the value between the startup phase and the public company phase.', '"Value,Company,Venture Capital"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Building product is not about having a large team to manage. It is about having a small team with the right people on it.', '"People,Building,Product"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"If you have a native monetization system where the atomic unit of content is the ad unit, that scales down all the way to a small screen experience. That\'s why Twitter is performing so well on mobile."', '"Experience,Way,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Many artists stick to making and hire a manager to focus on their business. Artists that build websites and mobile apps can do that, too."', '"Business,Focus,Build"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Not only do you have to put yourself in harms way in service of your country, you have to leave your families at home. It is a great sacrifice."', '"Home,Great,Sacrifice"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Venture capitalists are professional money managers. We are provided capital to invest as long as we can return it to our investors with a strong return in a reasonable amount of time. A strong return is three times cash on cash. A reasonable amount of time is ten years max.', '"Money,Time,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Skyping with your spouse works well enough, but apparently it is hard to get the kids to hang out on Skype for long."', '"Long,Enough,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"The venture business is a bit of an apprenticeship business, so the firm I worked for didn\'t let me make an investment until I was 30. That was probably a very smart thing."', '"Business,Me,Smart"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Most adults I know start their Internet session at Google, and most kids I know start their Internet session at either Facebook or MySpace."', '"Internet,Start,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Board meetings should not be for the benefit of the board. They should be for the benefit of the CEO and the senior team.', '"Meetings,CEO,Team"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Internet and mobile product development cycles are measured in months, not years. And the capital required to get a product built and into the market is less than $1 million. And the returns, when things work out, can be enormous."', '"Work,Internet,Development"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'I believe Android will be stronger in the developing world than it is in the developed world.', '"Believe,World,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Startups are rapidly changing systems. If you use an annual review cycle, you aren\'t getting feedback at the same pace that you need to adapt and change the business."', '"Change,Business,Review"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"My venture investing career has three phases, all roughly 6-8 years long. The first, at Euclid, was software to Internet. The second, at Flatiron, was Internet to bubble. And the third, at USV, has been web 2 to mobile. I have always used a new firm to denote a new investment phase for me. Throw away the old. Start with the new."', '"Me,Long,Internet"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"All markets have boom and bust cycles, and I think venture capital market has even more exaggerated boom and bust cycles."', '"More,Think,Venture Capital"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"The Web is going to capture an increasing share of people\'s attention, and billions of dollars are going to flow in. What Web 2.0 is about is harnessing those dollars in highly leverageable ways."', '"People,Attention,Flow"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"When my dad was in Vietnam, we lost a parent for a year. Thank God we didn\'t lose a parent for good."', '"God,Good,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Start-ups should be hunch-driven early on and data-driven as they scale.', '"Early,Scale,Should"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Certainly anything that is news or opinion needs to be free on the Web, because the Web is this very fluid medium that is very much driven by links and the flow of visitors through a discussion via links."', '"Free,News,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"When I see people laughing at ideas and companies we have backed, I smile. It means we are going to make a lot of money on that investment."', '"Smile,Money,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'One of the great things about young entrepreneurs is that they don\'t know that something can\'t be done. So they try something that\'s so audacious and usually end up pulling it off.', '"Great,Done,Great Things"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'I\'m a free speech bigot. I don\'t like censorship; I just don\'t think it\'s a good thing.', '"Good,Free,Censorship"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Twitter wasn\'t planned. It just happened.', '"Planned,Happened,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'It\'s upsetting to me that you have to be a millionaire to invest in your friend\'s start-up.', '"Me,Your,Friend"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"The more entrepreneurs in the world that are getting their ideas financed, the more great companies there are going to be that we can all invest in."', '"Great,World,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'To see things differently requires you to be wired a little differently.', '"See,Things,Little"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'I think \'crazy\' is a compliment. I think you make money with people who are crazy.', '"Money,Crazy,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'There is a difference between hiring a CEO and turning over control of the business.', '"Business,Control,Difference"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'The companies that do the best job on managing a user\'s privacy will be the companies that ultimately are the most successful.', '"Best,Privacy,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'So many folks in the venture capital business are sheep that just want to follow the herd. They are momentum investors purchasing highly illiquid investments. That is a recipe for disaster.', '"Business,Sheep,Disaster"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"We need new medical approaches to preventing and/or curing disease. We need new scientific approaches to generating, storing, and being more efficient with energy. Maybe we need more space exploration. Maybe we need more undersea exploration."', '"Space,Medical,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"I believe the mobile OS market will play out very similarly to Windows and Macintosh, with Android in the role of Windows. And so, if you want to be in front of the largest number of users, you need to be on Android."', '"Believe,Will,I Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Facebook is not an unstoppable juggernaut. There are a lot of other things people can do on the web.', '"People,Unstoppable,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Customers are a great way to finance a business for many reasons. First, customer financing is typically non dilutive. They want something from you other than equity in your business. Customers also help you fit your product to the market. And customers will help debug and improve the quality of the product."', '"Business,Great,Finance"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'The most common way customer financing is done is you sell the customer on the product before you\'ve built it or before you\'ve finished it. The customer puts up the money to build the product or finish the product and becomes your first customer. Usually the customer simply wants the product and nothing more.', '"Money,Way,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'It takes great salesmanship to convince a customer to buy something from you that isn\'t built or isn\'t finished.', '"Great,Buy,Customer"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Equity capital is expensive. Every time you do a raise, you dilute."', '"Time,Equity,Expensive"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Facebook, Twitter, and Tumblr are all \'User First, Brands Second\' services. The brands are all over these services now. But for the most part, these services didn\'t do much to bring them. The engaged users did."', '"First,Now,Bring"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'There are so many startups out there raising money. I don\'t think this is a bad thing. It\'s a good thing. Entrepreneurship is in vogue. Innovators are innovating. Makers are making.', '"Money,Good,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Being an entrepreneur is hard. Having supportive and caring investors helps.', '"Caring,Hard,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Investing in management means building communication systems, business processes, feedback, and routines that let you scale the business and team as efficiently as possible."', '"Business,Communication,Management"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"If you are successful, you will be cloned. That\'s life. In fact, it\'s a sign that you\'ve made it when clones of your website, mobile app, and business start cropping up."', '"Life,Business,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"The entire world is now a rival to Silicon Valley. No country, state, region, nor city has a lock on innovation in technology anymore."', '"Technology,World,City"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Given New York City\'s cultural diversity, it has always attracted creative people."', '"City,Diversity,New"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Games are the most social of all things on the web.', '"Social,Things,All Things"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Foursquare\'s adoption of a game dynamic when it launched is a particularly clever implementation of a social hook.', '"Game,Clever,Social"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Marketing is for companies who have sucky products.', '"Who,Marketing,Products"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Politics and government have been a terrible place to invest; education has been a terrible place to invest, but that is because the entrenched interests make it a terrible place to invest. The way you invest in those sectors is you go against the entrenched interests; you try and disrupt the entrenched interests, not to service them."', '"Education,Politics,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"New York\'s niche is content, and content is becoming more valuable. Just think about what is more valuable: MTV or the cable system that you use to get MTV? Howard Stern or the radio station you use to listen to him? Ultimately, technology becomes a commodity, and content - real, true branded content - becomes more valuable."', '"Technology,True,New"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"I don\'t like to talk about myself. I like to talk about stuff that\'s happening, stuff that\'s going to happen, and the people who are going to make it happen."', '"Myself,Make It Happen,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"When there were not very many Internet companies, the supply of Internet companies to the market was small and the appetite for them was large. Therefore, if you were in the business of creating Internet companies in 1996-98, you had a market that provided massive demand for that."', '"Business,Internet,Small"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"People already love to play casual games. But when you take a casual game and stick it inside a social network, it becomes way more exciting."', '"Love,Game,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"When people laugh at a company or say, \'This is the stupidest thing I have ever heard,\' you are listening."', '"People,Laugh,Listening"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Yahoo is free, it\'s fast and it\'s Web-centric. AOL is slow, it costs money and requires proprietary software."', '"Money,Free,Fast"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'The best talent in the venture industry doesn\'t work in large companies and won\'t work in large companies.', '"Work,Best,Talent"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'The Internet is a computing platform built on top of core technology. Applied technology is what gets built on top of that: It\'s Web services.', '"Technology,Internet,Top"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"I\'m not saying M.B.A.s can\'t be great entrepreneurs. They can. But you don\'t need a degree to figure out it\'s costing you $5,000 per month to run your business, so you need $30,000 to keep it going for six more months."', '"Business,Great,Degree"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Money is information, like bits."', '"Money,Information,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"It\'s not easy for an entrepreneur to find the time to blog. But for those who do it, it is a great tool to communicate with the various stakeholders in their business and build a reputation for thought leadership."', '"Leadership,Business,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"Blog-based businesses have lower cost structures and are more \'authentic,\' and as a result are drawing larger shares of ad budgets."', '"Result,Drawing,More"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'I would like to reiterate that I don\'t want any profiles of me. I am not newsworthy.', '"Me,I Am,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', 'Profiles aren\'t journalism.', '"Journalism,Profiles"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec5', '"I generally blog between 5:30 A.M. and 7 A.M. I will from time to time add something during the day, but for the most part blogging is an early morning activity for me."', '"Time,Morning,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec6', '"If human beings are fundamentally good, no government is necessary; if they are fundamentally bad, any government, being composed of human beings, would be bad also."', '"Good,Government,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec6', '"It seems like such a terrible shame that innocent civilians have to get hurt in wars, otherwise combat would be such a wonderfully healthy way to rid the human race of unneeded trash."', '"War,Way,Innocent"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec6', '"Government is an unnecessary evil. Human beings, when accustomed to taking responsibility for their own behavior, can cooperate on a basis of mutual trust and helpfulness."', '"Trust,Government,Responsibility"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', 'Rape is the only crime in which the victim becomes the accused.', '"Victim,Only,Which"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', '"Woman throughout the ages has been mistress to the law, as man has been its master."', '"Man,Law,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', '"There is another side to chivalry. If it dispenses leniency, it may with equal justification invoke control."', '"Control,Side,Equal"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', 'That man is a creature who needs order yet yearns for change is the creative contradiction at the heart of the laws which structure his conformity and define his deviancy.', '"Change,Heart,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', '"Stripped of ethical rationalizations and philosophical pretensions, a crime is anything that a group in power chooses to prohibit."', '"Power,Group,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', '"The Rubicons which women must cross, the sex barriers which they must breach, are ultimately those that exist in their own minds."', '"Women,Sex,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', 'The type of fig leaf which each culture employs to cover its social taboos offers a twofold description of its morality. It reveals that certain unacknowledged behavior exists and it suggests the form that such behavior takes.', '"Culture,Leaf,Behavior"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', '"The passionate controversies of one era are viewed as sterile preoccupations by another, for knowledge alters what we seek as well as what we find."', '"Knowledge,Find,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec7', 'Major social movements eventually fade into the landscape not because they have diminished but because they have become a permanent part of our perceptions and experience.', '"Experience,Permanent,Landscape"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I know how lucky I am, and I am aware that I have to fight the perception that I am also a spoiled brat."', '"Fight,I Am,Perception"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"People want to see me as a posh square, so I\'ll play an East End drag queen or a young man with a cleft palate."', '"Man,Me,Queen"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"The joy of being a chameleon on stage is that you can be anything, and yet you\'re not any of those things as well."', '"Joy,Chameleon,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I am a better cook now than I used to be.', '"I Am,Better,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"When I first looked at \'Travesties,\' I thought, \'I don\'t know what to make of the first page of this, let alone 80 pages.\' But I just thought, \'Well, I\'ll go along for the audition because I love all the people involved.\'"', '"Love,Alone,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I have learned already that you have to work against people\'s perception as they want to box you in very quickly.', '"Work,People,I Have Learned"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"My dad has never had a mobile phone or computer. And that was the way when I grew up, so I still take tech with a pinch of salt."', '"Dad,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I don\'t think you necessarily fall in love with a sexuality, I think you fall in love with a person."', '"Love,Sexuality,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I suppose what I look for most in a part, other than it being different than the part before, is: Does he interest me? Will I have fun getting to know him and, to a greater or lesser degree, physically embodying him?"', '"Look,Me,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"At drama school we were encouraged to keep fit and healthy, but not to bulk out. We were told to stay lithe to allow our bodies to morph when we\'re playing various parts. Running is ideal for this, especially when I needed a lean look for the Channel 4 drama \'Cucumber.\'"', '"Look,Drama,School"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I was drawn to gay parts because of their scripts, what the roles offered."', '"Gay,Because,Parts"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I want to have a very definite style that people recognise as being \'Fred Fox.\'', '"Style,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"My favourite film is \'Tootsie.\' I suppose that\'s because it\'s very much about my industry and I love all the jokes, albeit a slightly bygone age of the 1980s, a world that I really understand."', '"Love,Age,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"It gets me, physical comedy. There\'s nothing better than it."', '"Me,Better,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"On every job you learn, on every job you should be looking to learn and every decision you make on the jobs you take, they should always try in some way, even if not in a huge way, they should in some way stretch you."', '"Decision,Looking,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I don\'t really approach any part in any particular way. I tend to get an instinct on the way I want to do it, depending on that role."', '"Way,Want,Approach"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'My love of running developed when I got older. At school it filled me with dread and the idea of running around the sports pitches struck me with a nameless fear.', '"Love,Fear,Sports"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'It\'s part of my job as an actor to look after myself. Your appearance is crucial.', '"Myself,Look,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"The Dorset coast, where I spent my childhood, is a gorgeous place to run. I love to explore and revisit places like the cliffs at Kimmeridge Bay and the abandoned village of Tyneham."', '"Love,Childhood,Village"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"Umm, I used to stink-bomb peoples\' letterboxes on the weekends when their newspapers were delivered."', '"Used,Weekends,Were"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I was obsessive and made my parents take me to the hairdressers way more often than I needed to.', '"Me,Parents,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I used to read \'Dennis\' in the Beano when I went to have my hair cut.', '"Hair,Cut,Used"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I\'ve always wanted to work with Dad.', '"Work,Dad,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'We\'re into a world where we\'re not talking about gay or straight or bisexual any more so much as we\'re talking about being transgender or identifying as a woman if you\'re a man.', '"Man,World,Gay"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'Who\'s ready for anything when they\'re 21?', '"Anything,Ready"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'Dad hates London.', '"Dad,London,Hates"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'Costume is always the first layer of armour for going into battle in a new acting job.', '"Battle,New,Acting"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I adore clothes. More importantly, I admire people who dress well."', '"Dress,People,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I love a good suit, and when I see photographs of myself in a jacket that doesn\'t fit me quite right or the sleeves are too long, it drives me insane."', '"Love,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"No, I\'m not too worried about type casting."', '"About,Casting,Type"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I think each generation struggles with its own set of problems.', '"Problems,Generation,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I am delighted to be working with Guy Ritchie on \'King Arthur,\' who\'s been a boyhood hero of mine ever since \'Lock, Stock\' and \'Snatch.\'"', '"King,Hero,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'My dad did a wonderful feat of memory and storytelling by taking T S Eliot\'s \'Four Quartets\' on the road in a one-man show.', '"Dad,Memory,Road"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I love being on film sets even if I\'m not acting in the film, and I\'m fascinated by the work of the director of photography."', '"Love,Work,Acting"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I think it\'s dangerous being cynical because you close doors rather than open them.', '"Doors,Dangerous,Open"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I\'m not easily wound up, but overly cynical people irritate me."', '"Me,People,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I wouldn\'t wish to go \'I am this or I am tha\'because at some time in my life, yes I\'ve had girlfriends, but I might fall in love with a man."', '"Life,Love,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I\'m an entertainer, that\'s my business, and yet you hope at some point in your career you will do something that will mean more to people."', '"Hope,Business,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I was brought up in a bubble to an extent.', '"Bubble,Up,Extent"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I didn\'t really enter into the real world until I was probably at drama school.', '"World,Drama,School"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I\'m blessed and fortunate I met many people, like agents, who\'d take a meeting with me because my mum or dad would ask if they\'d see me."', '"Dad,Me,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"So often gay characters, particular those portrayed in an era where gayness was something of a taboo and a statement about \'who I am and no one\'s going to trample me down,\' are more colourful and interesting - and for an actor, that\'s enticing."', '"Me,I Am,Gay"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I think as an actor you\'ve got to try to preserve some of your mystery so that there\'s still an element of surprise about where characters come from.', '"Surprise,Mystery,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I\'ve been around actors all my life.', '"Life,My Life,Around"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"Now, I don\'t think I\'d particularly care if somebody criticised me for having got to a certain level of success because I\'m Ed Fox\'s and Joanna David\'s son. I know that\'s not true."', '"Success,Me,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I wanted to be a director of photography for a while, because I\'m fascinated by what they do. You\'re made to look good by them and you can learn so much from talking to them."', '"Good,Look,Photography"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'That\'s why I wanted to be an actor - to be everybody. Through all those different people I can learn about myself.', '"Myself,People,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'It would be silly for me to say I\'ll only ever love women. That would be crazy.', '"Love,Women,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"Everybody who I\'ve spoken to who was conscious when \'Queer as Folk\' went out says it was a complete game-changer. It completely changed people\'s perception of young, gay men especially."', '"Men,Gay,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"As actors, we have the best job in the world, but occasionally it can be made difficult by ego and by not listening to each other and lack of communication."', '"Best,Communication,World"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I do want people to think of me as an actor, not just a posh actor who does posh parts."', '"Me,People,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'If I keep doing films like \'The Riot Club\' they\'re going to think I\'m a posh git.', '"Doing,Club,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'Dad\'s mother and aunt were actresses.', '"Dad,Mother,Aunt"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I enjoyed throwing the toys out of the pram, although not in a petulant way."', '"Way,Toys,Enjoyed"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"There\'ll probably be moments in my life where it seems that people will want to camp out on my doorstep, and moments when no one wants to hire me and couldn\'t be less interested. I\'ve been around the circus, and it\'ll come and go."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I can neither change people\'s perceptions nor change my background, and nor would I wish to."', '"Change,People,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"As actors, you live in doubt; that\'s one of the truths of the particular job."', '"Live,Doubt,Job"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"All you ever want as an actor is to play psychologically complex, interesting characters and Jeremy Bamber is at the very least that."', '"Interesting,Want,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"Look, I certainly couldn\'t say that my unusual upbringing didn\'t lend itself to becoming an actor - of course it did. People want to see what Edward and Joanna\'s son can do."', '"Look,People,Son"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"Some people cannot stand up in front of people and talk, and I can - I think that\'s something you don\'t learn; you\'re born with it."', '"People,Stand,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I want to prove that I can be a success without standing on the shoulders of my family.', '"Success,Family,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I tried to work hard at school because I knew that my parents were paying a lot of money for it.', '"Work,Money,Parents"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"People balk at the fact that I\'ve played loads of gay characters. Maybe I have, but you know what? It doesn\'t matter."', '"Gay,People,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'Most of the independent films I\'ve been involved with all had European subsidy or co-production agreements.', '"Independent,Had,Involved"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'If I don\'t shave I look like a peach with fuzz on it - not a good look.', '"Good,Look,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'No one with a bad tie is getting my vote. Some Lib Dems wear the most shockingly awful ties.', '"Bad,Vote,Wear"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', '"I love the energy of Islington, the variety of things you can see, taste and buy, the number of young people around you all moving and bustling - yet it still feels like a village, a community."', '"Love,Community,Village"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec8', 'I\'m a man of eclectic and wide and broad taste.', '"Man,Taste,Eclectic"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'You\'re going to be friends with people longer than you\'re going to be teammates in this game.', '"Game,People,Teammates"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"When I played Little League, I looked up to the big leaguers, too, and collected their baseball cards."', '"Cards,Big,Baseball"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"In the past, my success has come with sticking to one plan. That usually works. Obviously it\'s going to falter, and I\'m going to go into slumps here and there, but stick with the plan, and hopefully it will come out successful more times than not."', '"Success,Past,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'There\'s nothing I can really do but keep going out there and swinging.', '"Keep Going,Nothing,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"When you come back on top after you\'ve fallen, it\'s a better story."', '"Better,Back,Story"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"It\'s just so much fun to relax and just play baseball for a living. It\'s a great time in my life. I\'m never going to forget it, and it\'s very humbling."', '"Life,Time,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Just got to keep going out there and keep swinging. That\'s all I can really do. Getting work in, doing everything I can to get ready for the game."', '"Work,Keep Going,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"It\'s something I\'d never wish anybody to have to go through, having a mother pass away at a young age. But it\'s made me realize that people need help."', '"Age,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I grew up an Angels fan.', '"Fan,Up,Angels"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I think this world needs a little more hugging in their lives.', '"World,More,Needs"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Growing up in California, I grew up a JT Snow fan."', '"Fan,Growing Up,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I love coming home.', '"Love,Home,Coming"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'You got to put the personal stuff away and see the business side of it.', '"Business,See,Side"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Leading off an inning you never know, I could get a bunt base hit and start a rally."', '"Start,Never,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I want to represent Canada so I can represent my mother.', '"Canada,I Can,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"For me, feeling good is line drives to left field."', '"Good,Me,Feeling Good"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I stick to what got me here and what I know best. That\'s the same routine. I\'m not going to vary it.', '"Best,Me,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"You think about when you\'re kids and see these guys on TV, and now you\'re in the same clubhouse as Chipper Jones and Bobby Cox."', '"Clubhouse,See,Now"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"They said if I could deal with the pain, I should play. So, I did, and for some reason, I started hitting. It was a weird thing. I don\'t know if it was because I couldn\'t do too much, and I was just trying to stay up through the middle and not hurt myself."', '"Myself,Pain,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Sometimes, you can get too big when you feel too good."', '"Good,Feel,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Usually, my track record\'s pretty good with guys on base."', '"Good,Pretty,Track"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Usually, I can get the job done with guys in scoring position."', '"Done,I Can,Position"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I would like to be out there every day and be that one steady guy that everybody can lean on.', '"Day,Every Day,Steady"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"I have one goal every single year, and that\'s to play every single game."', '"Game,Year,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Enjoy and have fun when you\'re a kid, because you are a kid."', '"Fun,Enjoy,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Just have fun, and just play hard, and just practice a lot."', '"Fun,Practice,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Thrilling, thrilling to see yourself on a baseball card for the first time."', '"Time,Yourself,First Time"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Coming in here and having fun with the guys, loving everyone, playing this game - it\'s a lot of fun."', '"Game,Fun,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"If I don\'t get hits, I don\'t get hits, but I\'m trying to get hits."', '"Trying,Get,Hits"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I\'m going to go out there and just keep trying to get better.', '"Better,Trying,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"I don\'t really watch video, but I see the replay; like when I do strike out, and I\'m walking back to the dugout, I look up and see if they do show the replay of me swinging and missing."', '"Look,Me,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"I\'ve never been a guy that\'s consistently hit home runs. It\'s always seemed to come, like, three or four in a week or two, and then I\'ll shut it down for a couple of weeks."', '"Home,Never,Three"', '2023-05-29 12:08:00', '2023-05-29 12:08:00'),
	('401663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"Obviously, being a first baseman, you\'re kind of expected to hit some home runs. Obviously, that goes into your head; it gets into my head a little bit."', '"Home,Your,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"I always like going to the West Coast. I don\'t know if it\'s a certain field, team, whatever it is, but I usually seem to do well here."', '"Know,Always,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"You\'ve just got to keep grinding, putting good ABs together; just stop trying to look at the record, your batting average. You\'ve got to go out there and just keep playing."', '"Good,Together,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I\'d like to finish my career as a Brave.', '"Brave,Finish,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I\'m one of those guys who loses weight during the season.', '"Who,Weight,Those"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'Darren Erstad was special to watch when he moved from center field from first base.', '"Special,First,Field"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'There are certain guys you just take from different teams that you watch.', '"Watch,Just,Take"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I think about my mom every day.', '"Mom,Day,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', 'I have a platform to be able to do something to help other people beat cancer.', '"People,Help,Beat"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fec9', '"When you lose a mother or father, it\'s still the hardest time of your life."', '"Life,Time,Lose"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m not trying to act like I\'m Superman or better than anybody else in the game. I\'m just telling my story, showing my strengths and weaknesses - as a human, as a person, as a man."', '"Man,Game,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I played wide receiver in high school; then I went to college at Ball State and played safety.', '"School,Safety,Ball"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"When everybody goes left, I\'m gonna go right most of the time."', '"Time,Go,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I wasn\'t fully aware of the things that Madlib did musically, but my manager put me up on game. I\'m not gonna act like I was a Madlib head when I wasn\'t. I didn\'t understand a lot of it at first. But it opened my mind to some things, and it\'s me bringing that gangster element to things that he does. It\'s like a perfect marriage."', '"Marriage,Me,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'It\'s in the American spirit to take advantage of an opportunity.', '"Opportunity,Spirit,American"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Everything don\'t work out for the best. You have to use a lot of those things as lessons in order to build yourself up.', '"Work,Best,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Ninety percent of the general public aren\'t gangstas, so all of the rappers aren\'t going to be gangstas."', '"Percent,Going,General"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Jeezy just recognized my grind, and I jumped on board with him to enhance it. Artistically, we\'re in the same mind frame. We come from very similar backgrounds - poverty. That\'s something that we can both relate to, something that we can convey in our music."', '"Music,Mind,Poverty"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m from Gary, Indiana, and everybody\'s damn near at the poverty level. It\'s a rough city to grow up in, and it\'s a modern-day ghost town."', '"Grow,City,Poverty"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"There\'s some dudes that did Gangsta Grillz tapes who probably weren\'t worthy of it - their label just put up the bread, or they did a favor."', '"Bread,Up,Worthy"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'This is the land of getting over. The land of second or even third chances; the land of doing whatever you have to do by any means necessary in order to fulfill the American Dream.', '"American Dream,Doing,American"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'ve been known not to bite my tongue.', '"Tongue,Bite,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I don\'t really know what a debut album is no more. As long as you got music on the streets, you\'ve debuted."', '"Music,Long,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I grew up on N.W.A., Geto Boys. My dad was listening to that."', '"Dad,Listening,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m a loyal dude.', '"Dude,Loyal"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I just have to go against the grain. I mean, I can be objective and do what I need to do, handle my everyday living, follow directions, etc. But there\'s something that\'s always been attracted to that taboo. It\'s been like that since I was a child."', '"Living,Always,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"The things I rap about are 100 percent real. But at the same time, I don\'t rap about those things to tear my city down. I give you the reality of what it is and what I been through and how it is living in those conditions in Gary, Ind."', '"Time,Reality,City"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Nobody else was saying what he said on air, and sometimes he pushed the envelope when he said the newest Jay Z line with a Michael Jordan highlight. But Stuart Scott was an artist."', '"Sometimes,Nobody,Air"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '\'Kind of Blue\' is one of the best records of all time. Miles\' use of space is something rap fans can definitely appreciate. Sometimes you have to let the track breathe and throw a melody in here and there. He never did too much on \'Kind of Blue.\' It\'s the perfect vibe.', '"Best,Space,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Lil Wayne makes good music. He\'s one of the best rappers.', '"Best,Good,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"My core thing is gangster rap, but a lot of my music is melodic and carries a message of survival."', '"Music,Gangster,Survival"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'d be a liar if I didn\'t say I learned things from Jeezy. Hell yeah, I took some things, some pluses and some minuses, do\'s and don\'ts."', '"Liar,Hell,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I wanted to be a gangsta from birth, not because of the music but moreso what I was seeing, what my uncles were doing. I was just fascinated with the street lifestyle from a young age."', '"Age,Music,Street"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '\'Pinata\' is a great rap record for jazz fans.', '"Great,Jazz,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Madlib isn\'t a beatmaker, he\'s a producer."', '"He,Producer"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'A lot of improvisation and freedom went into \'Pinata.\'', '"Freedom,Improvisation,Lot"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I study my competition for at least an hour a day. I get on the Internet, I look at what they doing, and then I look at ways to defeat them. I know their mixtapes track-by-track. I know some of their lyrics."', '"Look,Competition,Internet"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Scarface is my favorite rapper.', '"Favorite,Rapper"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I tried to watch \'Inception,\' but I fell asleep."', '"Tried,Watch,Inception"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m not a big video game dude though, but I like \'Madden.\'"', '"Game,Big,Dude"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'My TV stays locked at \'SportsCenter.\' That and \'Pardon the Interruption.\'', '"Locked,Pardon,Stays"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"He\'s been my number one influence. If you say Tupac didn\'t influence you, then you don\'t really need to be rapping because nobody evokes that kind of emotion on a track like Tupac does."', '"Influence,Nobody,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"You\'ve got a lot of Tupac clones, but I don\'t think I\'m one of them. I just think I give people a little piece of the feeling he gave them."', '"People,Feeling,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I like A$AP Rocky and his stuff - Kendrick too.', '"Like,Stuff,Too"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Probably dancing to Cassie\'s \'Me & U\' - That\'s my guilty pleasure.', '"Me,Pleasure,Guilty"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I always knew that I would be some type of public figure, but I never knew that it would be rapping, \'cause my dad sang: I saw him deal with the ills of the music industry, just on the outside looking in."', '"Music,Dad,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Eminem heard my music, and he didn\'t wanna take a meeting with me."', '"Music,Me,He"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I went to a Bulls game when it was still in Chicago Stadium before they built the United Center.', '"Game,Still,Stadium"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'The neck is not something you should have surgery on that much.', '"Something,Neck,Much"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'The Bears need to let me be GM.', '"Me,Need,Bears"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I still bump \'Smells Like Teen Spirit.\' I used to listen to it before all my football games.', '"Teen,Football,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I love Lil Wayne. I grew up on the Hot Boyz.', '"Love,Hot,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Drake makes some dope songs.', '"Dope,Some,Makes"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I don\'t like rap that doesn\'t have a story behind it.', '"Story,Behind,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"When you go to places like Gary and Detroit, you see the economic problem in this country and who it\'s really affecting."', '"Country,See,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I ain\'t never detached myself from Gary.', '"Myself,Never,Detached"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'ve always played that role in my family: the breadwinner.', '"Family,Always,Role"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"We have good, neighborly people in Gary."', '"Good,People,Gary"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Ain\'t nothin\' changed with me. I\'m Eastside Gary til I die.', '"Me,Die,Changed"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"When I first came in the game, I had a bunch of homies that rapped that was hanging around me just because I was getting the rap attention, and they felt they could feed off of that."', '"Me,Game,Attention"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I don\'t mind travelling. I\'m independent, so I gotta get on the grind."', '"Mind,Independent,Grind"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Tupac is definitely an icon. There\'ll never be another Tupac, so I\'m not gonna ever, ever try to fill those shoes. I\'m just gonna stay in my lane and be the best me that I can be."', '"Best,Me,Shoes"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Coming up in America in the \'80s and \'90s, we were not too far removed from slavery. People forget that."', '"America,People,Forget"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I remember I used to go school with guys who couldn\'t afford notebooks, pens, paper: the necessary tools needed in order to survive in school. It\'s a lot of kids in Gary who are at a disadvantage without that."', '"Remember,School,Survive"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Me separating from CTE - I\'m extremely happy about that because a lot of guys wrote me off, Jeezy included. He really wrote me off."', '"Me,Happy,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I ain\'t on no major. Everything independent. Either way it goes, I am doing me, and I am doing Freddie Gibbs."', '"Me,I Am,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I am the evil seed.', '"I Am,Evil,Seed"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I had a nightmare that I was mopping floors and that this Freddie Gibbs thing was all a dream.', '"Dream,Had,Floors"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I never took a dollar from Young Jeezy. No advance, nothing."', '"Nothing,Never,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I have a respect for Young Jeezy. But the reason things didn\'t work out for me and Young Jeezy was because our approach to the industry... My approach to the industry was a tad bit different than his. I wanted to approach my career a different way; he wanted to go a different way.', '"Work,Respect,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m not really comfortable with being on songs with cats I don\'t really know.', '"Know,Comfortable,Cats"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I think that with me and Madlib, I was never afraid to really experiment with his tracks and things."', '"Me,Never,Afraid"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I feel like with a lot of Madlib\'s beats, they are made for storytelling. I feel like when I\'m working on stuff with him, I can really get into the storytelling aspect mode of my flow."', '"Feel,I Can,Flow"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I like good music, whichever lane it comes out of. As long as it\'s dope, that is all that matters with me."', '"Good,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I feel like I influence more than just rap.', '"Influence,Feel,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m a common dude.', '"Dude,Common"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I don\'t like pre-written raps; I think it makes the song better if you listen to the beat first. In a sense, you have to make a marriage with the beat. I ride the beat, hear the flow of the drums, get the melody of my flow, and then from that point, it\'s a process of what I want to say."', '"Marriage,Ride,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I look at some of my fans at my show, and a lot of them look like they\'re straight out of a punk rock show. They like what I\'m coming across with. I had seen them same thing when I went to this Scarface show, so it lets me know that I\'m on the right track."', '"Look,Me,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m trying to bring gangster rap back to the forefront, like in the early \'90s."', '"Gangster,Back,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m not trying to obey the rules of radio.', '"Rules,Trying,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Just give me a mic, and I\'ll rock it."', '"Me,Rock,Mic"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"After I got dropped by Interscope, I knew in my heart that I had to fight back some way or not rap at all. I just took it upon myself to get myself where I needed to be."', '"Myself,Heart,Fight"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401745', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Sports is one of the keys to my life. It definitely kept me out of a lot of trouble and gave me a lot of discipline.', '"Life,Sports,Discipline"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401746', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'ve been engulfed in sports since I was a 2-year-old; I picked up any kind of ball - a basketball, baseball, football - I just loved to play something. I loved the energy of being in arenas and watching the game on TV."', '"Sports,Football,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401747', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"My father took me to a lot of sports events as a child, and our TV stayed on ESPN."', '"Sports,Me,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401748', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Stuart Scott was a hero.', '"Hero,Scott,Stuart"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401749', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I just want to put my stamp on all kinds of music. Everything I do is going to be gangsta rap, street-based, street-oriented."', '"Music,Everything,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401750', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m cool with doing shows with 2,000 people. I don\'t have to rap in a stadium. As long as I can provide for my family and my art and live comfortably and live well, then I\'m good."', '"Cool,Family,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401751', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m like LeBron, man. I\'m like a smaller LeBron. That\'s why I\'m not in the NBA. If I had about five, six more inches, I\'d be in the league."', '"Man,Why,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401752', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'ve been interested in basketball since I was a little kid - like, 3. The Bulls were my team. If you grew up in Gary, the Bulls were everybody\'s team."', '"Up,Like,Basketball"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401753', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m just glad we get to see old records being broken. That\'s what sports is all about.', '"Sports,See,Broken"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401754', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I started hustling in early adolescence.', '"Adolescence,Early,Started"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401755', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I never write a song before I get the track because I just feel that I have to make a marriage with that track with my raps. And if it\'s something that\'s already there, it ain\'t gone really fit, I don\'t think."', '"Marriage,Song,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401756', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Gary is a old factory town right outside Chicago. From my standpoint, my family migrated there in the \'50s and \'60s from Mississippi - Sardis, Mississippi - shout out to Sardis, Mississippi. My family migrated there just like a lot of black families in that area: they migrated there to get jobs, to get those factory jobs, that steel mill job."', '"Family,Black,Steel"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401757', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"Every project might only sell like 30 to 50,000, but I mean, I\'m getting seven, eight dollars every CD. I make more money per record than an artist on a major label - I can definitely say that."', '"Money,I Can,Project"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401758', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I\'m so hands-on and involved in my own music that I feel like if I put the same effort into another artist, then I can definitely cultivate something great."', '"Music,Great,Effort"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401759', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"If you say your product is the best, back that up."', '"Best,Back,Product"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401760', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'d be quiet as a mouse if I didn\'t have the correct feeling about my music. I feel like I\'m able to talk about it and say I\'m one of the best because I think I got the music to back that up. I got the live show to back that up. That\'s all that matters.', '"Best,Music,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401761', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I always want everything I do to be somewhat cinematic. I don\'t want to be the rapper that\'ll just post up and shoot a video anywhere with no real meaning to it.', '"Real,Always,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401762', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I think that \'Pinata\' album is going to stand the test of time. It\'s going to be a moment in hip-hop, whether people know it or not. It\'s nothing else like that in rap. It\'s going to forever hold its place."', '"Time,Moment,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401763', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I always feel like the underdog.', '"Feel,Underdog,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401764', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I can do a whole project with Madlib and turn around and do a record with Gucci Mane. Gucci Mane, E-40, and Black Thought on the same record. I like all those rappers, so why can\'t I work with them in some type of capacity? It just speaks to my versatility. I don\'t just listen to one type of rap. I listen to all of it so I can make all of it."', '"Work,Black,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401765', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"I feel like some artists need a record label, and some don\'t."', '"Feel,Need,I Feel Like"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401766', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Gary is a really impoverished town; it\'s in industrial decay. There\'s low employment and things of that nature.', '"Nature,Things,Employment"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401767', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I don\'t ever really plan my sets. I just get out there and feel the energy of the crowd.', '"Energy,Feel,Plan"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401768', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I wanted to be in the NBA. I wanted to be in the NFL.', '"Wanted,NBA,NFL"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401769', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', '"My mom had me at a young age, like 20, and she was the oldest child. All her brothers were seven and 10, so I was like a younger brother more so than the oldest child. I was the younger brother to all my uncles, so they were going through their childhood and their teenage years, and I was right there."', '"Age,Mom,Childhood"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401770', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I\'m an educated individual.', '"Educated,Individual"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401771', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'Different rappers got different talents. It\'s like X-Men.', '"Like,Talents,Got"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401772', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feca', 'I want to be one of the most versatile rappers in the game.', '"Game,Want,Versatile"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401773', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I like all sorts of chocolate. Milk chocolate, dark chocolate, anything."', '"Dark,Chocolate,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401774', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'For every different role you play it\'s nice to have different challenges for each one.', '"Challenges,Nice,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401775', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I\'m sure everyone has many types of music that they enjoy.', '"Music,Everyone,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401776', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I\'m not a sad person, upset the whole time, but I seem to be quite emotional."', '"Sad,Time,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401777', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I\'ve got a good family to support me, so I\'m grounded in that way."', '"Family,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401778', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I like to go to bed early so I can get up early.', '"I Can,Bed,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401779', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I guess I\'m just a normal kid apart from the acting.', '"Acting,Normal,Guess"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401780', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I\'ve never been a great cook.', '"Great,Never,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401781', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I never really acted at school. It was doing small parts on TV that really got me started.', '"Me,School,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401782', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I always tend to see, right after reading the script, the character and how I want to play it. I guess that\'s sort of most of the work, preparing for the role, but almost the creation of the character seems to go on as I read through the script."', '"Work,Character,See"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401783', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"\'Cinema Paradiso\' is a fantastic film, I love that."', '"Love,Cinema,Film"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401784', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I have a younger brother.', '"Brother,Younger,Younger Brother"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401785', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'Scary is good. Kids like going to a movie and being really scared rather than fake scared.', '"Good,Fake,Scared"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401786', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'There\'s never been a particular band that I\'ve followed religiously. But I do tend to listen to sadder music.', '"Music,Never,Band"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401787', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'Don\'t get too set on becoming an actor at an early age. I think that\'s where some people get into trouble. Acting becomes their life. I don\'t want that.', '"Life,Age,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401788', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"When you\'re happy you don\'t always have to be laughing, and when you\'re sad you don\'t have to be crying; sometimes it\'s the opposite. You laugh when you\'re the most upset."', '"Sad,Laugh,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401789', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'Johnny Depp is probably the best actor.', '"Best,Actor,Johnny Depp"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401790', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I\'m pretty rubbish, as we say in Britain, artwise, and I always envy people who can pick up something and even do just a little doodle of someone that looks vaguely like them. It\'s impressive."', '"People,Envy,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401791', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'People build up a picture of Johnny Depp as being some sort of weird pirate character. In reality he\'s incredibly nice... one of the nicest people I\'ve ever met.', '"Character,Reality,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401792', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'Every day is a different day in New York; there\'s always something new going on.', '"Day,New,Every Day"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401793', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I like hot weather. I think it might be a bit better if England was a bit hotter.', '"Weather,Hot,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401794', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'I wish I could draw.', '"Wish,I Wish,Could"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401795', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I think in some ways I\'m quite lucky to be living in London, there\'s this certain separation from the movie business. In that way, it\'s been quite easy to separate acting and going back to a normal life."', '"Life,Business,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401796', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"As always, with acting, you can\'t be too self-conscious. You shouldn\'t care about what people are thinking about you at the time because they\'re not caring about you, they\'re caring about the character."', '"Time,Character,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401797', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"People have different expectations when you\'re younger - it\'s less about changing yourself into a character; they want a more natural thing. And they just want you to be able to turn up every day and carry on working. They have a horrible fear of 10- or 11-year-olds, that they\'re going to say \'I don\'t want to play today.\'"', '"Fear,Today,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401798', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', 'It\'s very nice having my mum as my agent. You know that she\'s always doing what\'s best for you.', '"Best,Know,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401799', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecb', '"I think a lot of the time having someone who you, not base yourself on, but can see yourself being after a few years, you can get quite blinded by that, in the same way love can be."', '"Love,Time,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401800', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'I advise all the young kids to not overwork. You can\'t be out there blowing hard. You have to pace yourself.', '"Yourself,Young,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401801', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"That was the biggest thrill, going over to these guy\'s houses and having them want me to practice with them and they would show me a lot of stuff, which was really advanced stuff to me at my age."', '"Age,Me,Practice"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401802', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"When I got started in New York, it wasn\'t like it is now. If you were different from Miles and Dizzy, it was very difficult to make gigs and make money with your own style."', '"Money,Style,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401803', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'Dizzy used to tell me that I am playing too hard. He used to say to not give everything. Miles used to tell me that too.', '"Me,I Am,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401804', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'I am in discussions with a label. We are talking about doing something.', '"I Am,Doing,Talking"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401805', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"I had heard Ornette a couple of times, but I didn\'t really know where he was coming from until we started the record and it was beautiful, Fred. It opened up my mind."', '"Beautiful,Mind,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401806', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"I quit drinking, so I can think clear. When you have chop trouble, drinking doesn\'t help the healing process."', '"Process,Help,Healing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401807', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'I\'m going to Yoshi\'s. I\'m taking a few gigs. I\'m playing. I\'m not going to play all the time. I\'m going to take it easy and take it slow and warm up so I can come back.', '"Time,Back,Slow"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401808', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'They always want to sell me as a hard bopper.', '"Me,Always,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401809', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', 'We all kind of grew up together with Art Blakey because we all were young and he gave us a chance to write. We had to write something that was good and to sit up with a great guy like Art Blakey and watch him.', '"Good,Art,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401810', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"Well, my sister played trumpet. Can you imagine having a sister blowing the trumpet around the house, Fred? And my brother, he played piano. Everybody was playing some kind of music, so it was natural for me to get into it."', '"Music,Me,House"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401811', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecc', '"Yes, I can play. I can play. I can\'t play as long as I did and as hard, but I don\'t think I have to."', '"Long,I Can,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401812', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I was an underwear model for Calvin Klein for a few years. It is not something I wanted to do at first. I never regretted it, but I am a shy person, and to stand there buck naked in front of a camera was scary."', '"I Am,Naked,Shy"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401813', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I have a house with its own dock and I can take my boat out when I want.', '"Boat,I Can,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401814', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I had hip surgery in America because I\'d had problems during my last two years in Europe. They said out there that my hip was broken and I didn\'t know about it.', '"Problems,America,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401815', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"When I came from Europe, I was told that Americans don\'t care about soccer and this and that. But the way people cared was beyond my wildest expectations. You can\'t manufacture that."', '"Expectations,Care,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401816', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I break out in a rash if I go to the gym; all I did was shave my chest.', '"Go,Gym,Break"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401817', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Where I am from in Sweden was on the beach, so I love the sound of the water hitting the dock."', '"Love,Water,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401818', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I lived on being a quick player and my hamstring was breaking every time I made a quick move. I wondered what the hell was going on.', '"Time,Hell,Quick"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401819', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I didn\'t know exactly what to expect when I first came to Seattle but I have to say that how the city and the fans have embraced me has gone beyond my wildest dreams and for that I am forever grateful.', '"Dreams,Me,City"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401820', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Some people thought I was crazy when I quit Europe to go to the U.S., but for me the quality of life and the place I live is important."', '"Life,Me,Quality"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401821', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'What I say in the dressing room always stays there.', '"Always,Room,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401822', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Real Madrid\'s Bernabeu was an amazing stadium to play in. It was just on top of you, and such a big stadium."', '"Amazing,Real,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401823', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I am not particularly disciplined, but I am stubborn like few."', '"I Am,Stubborn,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401824', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"As a child I could lie in bed and do absolutely nothing for hours but once I decided to do something, big or small, I could not stop until it had been completed."', '"Lie,Nothing,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401825', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I played against Ashley Cole all the time in training. For me, he is the best left-back in the world. He was the hardest opponent and I had him every day in training."', '"Best,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401826', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'It takes time to know what makes an individual player tick.', '"Time,Know,Individual"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401827', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I made a conscious decision when I was about 30 that I wanted to do something different with my life. I felt a little bit lost and didn\'t trust people, so I decided to move to America."', '"Life,Trust,Decision"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401828', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I like entertaining football but, at the same time, you can\'t concede goals. That\'s a tricky balance to find."', '"Time,Football,Goals"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401829', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"For me, happy footballers play the best football."', '"Best,Football,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401830', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I am not a big gym fan.', '"I Am,Big,Fan"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401831', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I played team handball when I was a child. It is a very brutal sport.', '"Child,Team,Brutal"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401832', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"When friends come over from Europe, they think it\'s going to be rainy in Seattle but it\'s beautiful. It\'s a hidden pearl. And people here respect your private life."', '"Life,Respect,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401833', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I think it\'s important to learn about the culture of the place where you live.', '"Culture,Important,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401834', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Where I came from had a lot of friends. A big social circle.', '"Circle,Big,Social"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401835', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I played as a 10 and, in Sweden, they let me take as many touches as I could. All of a sudden, I come to Arsenal and I have to play one and two touches - it was a little bit alien to me."', '"Me,Alien,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401836', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Unai is very calm, composed and extremely detailed in what he expects. From Monday through to Friday, every single training session is very carefully planned."', '"Training,Calm,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401837', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I do my job - I don\'t try to seek the spotlight; that\'s not my way.', '"Way,Job,Try"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401838', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"When I went to Arsenal, people in Sweden said my game was more suited for Spain or Italy."', '"Game,People,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401839', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I felt, and it may sound a bit stupid, that I want to try things that are hard."', '"Stupid,Sound,Hard"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401840', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I\'m really excited by this opportunity to continue helping develop and work with some of the great young players we have coming through in the first-team environment and to work alongside Unai and his coaching team to help Arsenal win trophies.', '"Work,Great,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401841', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I felt Arsenal had let a lot of players go. When Thierry left I felt it was time for me to do something different and challenging.', '"Time,Me,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401842', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'West Ham have a great academy.', '"Great,Academy,West"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401843', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"The important thing for me is we want to keep the ball, we want to have the ball because we are Arsenal football club."', '"Football,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401844', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'What I try to focus on is going forward.', '"Focus,Try,Forward"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401845', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I think Unai did a great job and was a great leader, and a fantastic coach."', '"Great,Job,Leader"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401846', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Everyone that works knows that work is hard sometimes.', '"Work,Sometimes,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401847', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I go from day to day and game to game.', '"Game,Day,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401848', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'That\'s what it\'s all about. To play better. To win. There\'s nothing else to it.', '"Better,Win,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401849', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'My roles for Arsenal and Sweden are very different.', '"Sweden,Different,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401850', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'It is up to the coaches to tell me how to play.', '"Me,Tell,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401851', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'The Swedish team plays very differently from Arsenal. There is more freedom with Arsenal and they play a passing game.', '"Freedom,Game,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401852', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Sweden usually don\'t play good against the poor teams. We like being the underdogs.', '"Good,Poor,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401853', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"If you want to play at Arsenal you need to be top, top, you need precision."', '"Need,Precision,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401854', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I like it in Seattle.', '"Like,Seattle"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401855', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"You can see players do things in training that aren\'t a problem but they can\'t in a game situation. You have to work on it, relax and be brave."', '"Work,Relax,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401856', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I try to see what the players can do and not what they can\'t do.', '"See,Try,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401857', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Sometimes you have to just plug away, plug away in your game of football and maybe when your opponent gets a bit more tired you get that little extra metre and that\'s when you score the goals."', '"Football,Tired,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401858', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I am not that shy.', '"I Am,Shy,Am"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401859', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I\'ve always been interested in clothes and shopping, and I have a few friends who work in fashion."', '"Work,Shopping,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401860', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"But I\'m constantly surprised by the amount of interest in how I look. It\'s flattering, but a little weird - at the end of the day, I\'m a footballer."', '"Look,End Of The Day,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401861', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I had a coach when I was younger who encouraged me to be myself, that is where I was lucky."', '"Myself,Me,Lucky"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401862', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"The problem in Sweden is that, when the players are younger, they are not allowed to develop their own style and skills."', '"Style,Own,Players"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401863', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'You can be yourself in London. If you are a bit different in the way you dress or look it is no problem.', '"Be Yourself,Look,Dress"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401864', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I have always dressed to please myself, not other people. I don\'t care what they think."', '"Myself,Care,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401865', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'There were a lot of reasons why I wanted to leave Arsenal.', '"Why,Leave,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401866', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Clubs have always wanted to buy me during the summer but I have always stayed loyal because I wanted to stay at Arsenal.', '"Me,Summer,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401867', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I won almost everything there is to win and I look back with great memories.', '"Great,Memories,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401868', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Every time I sprinted 100 per cent, my hamstring broke. But I knew if I didn\'t sprint 100 per cent, I could keep on playing, so that\'s what you do. I was just lucky it was discovered in America and I haven\'t had one problem since. I feel I can run past people again and that feels nice."', '"Time,Past,America"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401869', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"When I went to Seattle, it was quite a quiet town and we made it the biggest soccer following in America. We didn\'t have the paparazzi, though, and I needed that at the time."', '"Time,America,Paparazzi"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401870', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'One thing I\'ve learned is that you have to be open-minded.', '"One Thing,Open-Minded,Learned"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401871', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I don\'t want to sound bigheaded or anything, but when you reach a certain level of recognition or fame, or whatever you want to call it, when you\'re young the first couple of years you think, \'Oh, this is fun.\'"', '"Fun,Young,Fame"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401872', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"If there\'s a back door somewhere, I take it. I try to get about without being noticed."', '"Door,Back,Somewhere"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401873', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I like my privacy.', '"Privacy,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401874', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'I went to West Ham in order to play against Arsenal as often as possible.', '"Possible,Order,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401875', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'And at West Ham no one gives you a puzzled look if you get called up for your national team and players are never asked to play on injections.', '"Look,Never,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401876', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"Wenger simply doesn\'t like those who show a weakness. With him you generally feel as if you were in the army. It\'s only in public that he may appear to be some sort of man of liberal views. In reality, his credo is natural selection."', '"Reality,Man,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401877', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Arsenal showed the door to too many people. Why did they let Thierry Henry go? When I found out about his move I realised the Arsenal I played for were finished.', '"Door,People,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401878', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I loved my time in Japan, and I am grateful to have had the chance to live in Japan and embrace the Japanese culture."', '"Time,Chance,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401879', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"I had to have tests for cancer and other diseases - it wasn\'t much fun. I was getting a shooting pain in my hip and we didn\'t know what it was. First of all we thought it was an old injury. But they didn\'t find anything wrong, even though when I had an ultrasound test it was all really swollen."', '"Pain,Fun,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401880', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', 'Sometimes when you play on the wing it gets a bit isolated and you can\'t help as much. But if you play a bit more central I can get the ball a lot more and help a lot more.', '"Sometimes,Help,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401881', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecd', '"When you play against a Spanish team, especially Madrid, it is quite an open game."', '"Game,Open,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401882', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I won\'t be a rock star. I will be a legend.', '"Legend,Rock Star,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401883', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"Money may not buy happiness, but it can damn well give it!"', '"Happiness,Money,Damn"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401884', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I\'m just a musical prostitute, my dear."', '"Just,Dear,Musical"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401885', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"When I\'m dead, I want to be remembered as a musician of some worth and substance."', '"Dead,Worth,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401886', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I always knew I was a star And now, the rest of the world seems to agree with me."', '"Me,World,Rest"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401887', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I dress to kill, but tastefully."', 'Dress', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401888', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"What will I be doing in twenty years\' time? I\'ll be dead, darling! Are you crazy?"', '"Time,Crazy,Dead"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401889', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I like to be surrounded by splendid things.', '"Surrounded,Things,Splendid"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401890', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"The reason we\'re successful, darling? My overall charisma, of course."', '"Reason,Successful,Course"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401891', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'When the whole point of Queen was to be original.', '"Queen,Be Original,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401892', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I\'m very emotional; I think I may go mad in several years\' time.', '"Time,Mad,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401893', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I want to lead the Victorian life, surrounded by exquisite clutter."', '"Life,Surrounded,Lead"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401894', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'A concert is not a live rendition of our album. It\'s a theatrica! event.', '"Live,Album,Concert"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401895', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"Onstage, I am a devil. But I\'m hardly a social reject."', '"Devil,I Am,Social"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401896', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"Years ago, I thought up the name Queen. It\'s just a name. But it\'s regal, obviously, and -sounds splendid."', '"Queen,Name,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401897', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"We\'re a very expensive group; we break a lot of rules. It\'s unheard of to combine opera with a rock theme, my dear ."', '"Rules,Rock,Group"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401898', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"Is Billy Idol just doing a bad Elvis pout, or was he born that way?"', '"Bad,Way,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401899', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"We\'re a bit flashy, but the music\'s not one big noise."', '"Music,Big,Noise"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401900', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"Back in the old days, we were often compared to Led Zeppelin. If we did something with harmony, it was the Beach Hoys. Something heavy was Led Zeppelin."', '"Harmony,Back,Old Days"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401901', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I\'m hopeless with money; I simply spend what I\'ve got.', '"Money,Hopeless,Simply"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401902', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'Who wants to live forever?', '"Live,Forever,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401903', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I have fun with my clothes onstage; it\'s not a concert you\'re seeing, it\'s a fashion show."', '"Fun,Fashion,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401904', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'We\'ve gone overboard on every Queen album. But that\'s Queen.', '"Queen,Gone,Album"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401905', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I think my melodies are superior to my lyrics.', '"Think,Lyrics,Superior"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401906', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"It destroys the soul to hear that you\'re all hype, that you have no talent, and that your whole career has been contrived."', '"Soul,Talent,Hype"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401907', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"We were disliked by the press in the early days because they couldn\'t put their finger on us, and that was the case with Zeppelin as well."', '"Well,Us,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401908', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'One night Roger was in a foul mood and he threw his entire bloody drumset across the stage. The thing only just missed me - I might have been killed.', '"Night,Me,Mood"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401909', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"The lavish presentation appeals to me, and I\'ve got to convince the others."', '"Me,Others,Lavish"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401910', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I was never too keen on the British music press. They\'ve called us a supermarket hype, and they used to suggest that we didn\'t write our own songs."', '"Music,Never,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401911', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"If we\'re weird onstage, I don\'t know what you\'d call the Tubes."', '"Weird,Know,Call"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401912', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"I got my diploma from Ealing College of Art, in graphics and illustration."', '"Art,Diploma,College"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401913', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"You know, I designed the Queen crest. I simply combined all the creatures that represent our star signs-and I don\'t even believe in astrology."', '"Believe,Queen,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401914', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"And, we have no such thing as a budget anymore. Our manager freaks when we show him the bill. We\'re lavish to the bone, but all our money goes back into the product."', '"Money,Back,Product"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401915', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I guess I\'ve always lived the glamorous life of a star. It \'s nothing new - I used to spend down to the last dime.', '"Life,New,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401916', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"But, you know, we spent two years putting our act together."', '"Together,Know,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401917', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', 'I\'m not into business at all.', 'Business', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401918', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"In the early days, we just wore black onstage. Very bold, my dear. Then we introduced white, for variety, and it simply grew and grew."', '"Black,Bold,White"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401919', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fece', '"The others don\'t like my interviews. And frankly, I don\'t care much for theirs."', '"Care,dont Care,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401920', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', 'I must end it. There is no hope. I will be at peace. No one had anything to do with it. My decision totally.', '"Hope,Peace,Decision"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401921', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"When I was little I was always getting hit. Kids would take my hat and throw it around, and it upset me. So I got to be very revengeful."', '"Me,Hat,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401922', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"I was mugged when I was 12. I had a portable radio, and I ran into this building and these two guys came in and hit me, busted me up and took the radio. After that I was very paranoid and I started taking kung fu and karate. But I didn\'t want to fight."', '"Fight,Me,Building"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401923', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"In fourth grade I had a high school reading level, but I didn\'t want to go to school and I didn\'t feel I belonged there."', '"Feel,School,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401924', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"I was in seventh grade at St. Matthew\'s. The teachers would tell me, \'God loves you,\' and then whack a ruler across my hand. \'Well,\' I\'d say, \'if God loves me, can you call God? Can you ask Him if it\'s all right that I didn\'t do my homework? If it\'s not, then let Him hit me.\'"', '"God,Me,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401925', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"I couldn\'t fight, and I wasn\'t particularly interested in the academic. So I started doing satiric bits in the school bathroom. Guys would cut class to come and see me."', '"Fight,Me,School"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401926', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fecf', '"But the only comparison that I want to Lenny Bruce is that I\'m funny. I\'m Freddie Prinze, Puerto Rican all the way."', '"Funny,Way,Comparison"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401927', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', 'Education has always been very important to me.', '"Education,Me,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401928', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', 'I left Facebook after Facebook groups began appearing about me and suddenly your personal photographs start becoming public property.', '"Me,Start,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401929', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"If my dramatic career doesn\'t work out, I will go on to research and find cures for Alzheimer\'s or Parkinson\'s and other motor neuron diseases. It\'s a very exciting field of research. But I\'d like to continue in drama, so it wouldn\'t be very smart of me if I blew this amazing opportunity with an inappropriate lifestyle."', '"Work,Amazing,Opportunity"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401930', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"I would most like to do film or TV. Possibly theatre in the future, but I\'m in L.A. a lot of the time at the moment and if I was going to do theatre it would be in London."', '"Future,Time,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401931', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"I really enjoyed my degree, for me it was the best course you can do. To be able to study the brain and nervous system and the mind with a scientific approach is just incredible! Its philosophical, psychological and biological, three very interesting areas to me."', '"Best,Brain,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401932', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"I think it\'s really important for your mental health to think about the big questions, to discuss them and open your mind, in order to prepare you for both life and death."', '"Life,Health,Death"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401933', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"What attracted me to acting, from the start, was playing different characters. I\'m not a massive fan of just playing myself on screen."', '"Myself,Me,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401934', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"If you can play lots of different characters, that\'s fun. As long as the material is good, that\'s what the attraction is for me."', '"Good,Me,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401935', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"It was fun playing a horrible, snotty kid in \'Harry Potter\', and then playing Prince Charming where I was also singing and playing guitar, and then playing a completely different character."', '"Character,Guitar,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401936', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"There are plenty of actors who\'ve caught the singing bug and vice versa, but with musical performers, you\'re constantly a persona - which is something I love about acting: you play a character, you leave and you get to be yourself again."', '"Love,Character,Be Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401937', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"Americans always ask how much I love my accent, and I don\'t get that - I think I sound like a school teacher."', '"Love,Teacher,School"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401938', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"In England, I suppose I have been known to once or twice tune into \'Big Brother\', which is a pretty terrible guilty pleasure."', '"Pleasure,Big,Guilty"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401939', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"Acting. It\'s the number one thing I love to do. That\'s why when people ask me what else I\'d love to do, I have no answer - this is all I ever wanted to do."', '"Love,Me,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401940', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', '"I\'ve got a pretty close bond with everyone in my family. I\'ve got a brother and a sister whom I\'m very close to, and my parents have always been the world\'s best parents."', '"Best,Family,World"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401941', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed1', 'I never remember my dreams.', '"Dreams,Remember,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401942', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Straight-up digital delivery will be the way the future works.', '"Future,Way,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401943', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Everyone talks about, \'Get your foot in the door,\' but I never understood that mentality. Why would I want to go in that house? Why not build my own house? Why not take a chair and smash a window?"', '"Window,Door,Chair"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401944', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'I don\'t think a lot of people really know what goes into something that they see.', '"People,See,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401945', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Film gives us the luxury of deciding where the viewpoint of the audience is, and by knowing that, we can very effectively design around what is actually seen on camera."', '"Design,Camera,Luxury"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401946', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'The goal is not to just do \'Video Game High School\' every year. We want to grow into a real content production company. We want to be Pixar or HBO. We want to make five series a year or 10 series a year.', '"Game,Grow,School"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401947', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"A lot of people have difficulty wrapping their heads around what VR is good for. And the direction people go first is wrong. The wrong place is always: How can we do something we\'ve done before, but on this?"', '"Good,Direction,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401948', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"I get occasional tweets from people asking what shampoo and conditioner I use. I go straight for the Costco brand, Kirkland brand, the bulk shampoo. That\'s as far as I go."', '"People,Go,Far"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401949', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"VR has a whole range of things it\'s very good at, and there\'s a lot of things that it\'s going to be deficient at."', '"Good,Things,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401950', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Non-studio entities can experiment with storytelling that might be too niche... for a studio.', '"Experiment,Storytelling,Studio"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401951', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"The moment you\'ve brought a toothbrush to work, then you\'re getting into crunch time."', '"Work,Time,Moment"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401952', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"At the end of the day, we still make the things that we make. And we found that the best strategy in this very fluid marketplace is to not be tied into any given platform, but to be able to make good content, and good content will be able to live anywhere."', '"Best,Good,End Of The Day"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401953', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Thanks to Netflix and Hulu, people are getting more and more used to consuming longer stretches of content on their televisions or computer screens."', '"People,Netflix,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401954', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"I feel like we cheated... because you read about these other directors, just like, \'Damn! They paid dues for 10 years before they got to get behind the camera.\' We cheated because technology was in the right place at the right time, and we were alive at the right age at the right time for us to take advantage of that."', '"Time,Age,Technology"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401955', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Five years is a very long time. If you think about it in terms of just people\'s lives, in terms of who our audience is: if you were in high school when you first saw our stuff, you\'re in college now."', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401956', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"There\'s a lot of history here. In terms of Asians in this country, you have a big influx after the Cultural Revolution, a big influx after the Korean War, a big influx after the Vietnam War."', '"War,History,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401957', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Views online is a real weird and sticky subject. One view on a 30-second piece of content is not equivalent to one view on a 30 minute video. In my mind it\'s not quite the same thing.', '"View,Mind,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401958', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"It\'s rare to find a corporate partner who encourages true creativity, but our meetings with Lionsgate\'s creative team convinced us that this is the right move for RocketJump and our millions of fans."', '"Meetings,Creativity,True"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401959', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"I don\'t think any reasonable person would object to you, as the advertiser, having say in who and what you want to pair your ad with."', '"Person,Your,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401960', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We have full creative control, we have a giant audience that loves what we do, and we can make whatever we want."', '"Control,Whatever,Audience"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401961', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"People predicted in the 1910s that live theater was going to be all gone and that we\'d just be watching movies. No, live theater is still around, because it does things that are specific to it."', '"Movies,People,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401962', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Deep engagement is much more powerful and valuable than fleeting mass market engagement.', '"More,Valuable,Fleeting"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401963', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We were looking for representation that was creatively and commercially in synch with our core DNA. The team at WME understands where we\'re going, and we\'re looking forward to taking our company to the next level with them by our side."', '"Looking Forward,Looking,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401964', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'I\'m not even very good at most video games.', '"Good,Video Games,Even"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401965', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Defying genre conventions is instantly a risky move.', '"Move,Genre,Risky"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401966', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"As you reach more people, there is a potential to make a living with what you are creating, and that\'s the goal."', '"People,Living,More"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401967', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Online is another way for all of us to reach people.', '"Way,People,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401968', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Shooting on location and dressing locations in Los Angeles is shockingly expensive, especially when you\'re talking about webseries-level budgets, so the opportunity to build our sets in YouTube\'s space gives us a lot more room in our budget in being able to create the world of \'VGHS\' properly."', '"Space,Opportunity,World"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401969', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'YouTube\'s a funny place because so many creators fall into their aesthetics out of necessity and the visuals are driven out of an urge to create. You get a lot of interesting examples of interesting design choices that have roots in practicality as well as an artistic sentiment.', '"Funny,Design,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401970', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'If you can\'t answer the question \'What is VR adding to that experience?\' - and it should be more than just a gee-whiz thing - then that project shouldn\'t be in VR. You\'re not taking full advantage of your medium.', '"Experience,Project,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401971', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Gamer humor ranges all over the place. What it comes down to is taking a lot of what we see in gaming and we\'re familiar with in gaming and being like, \'OK, hold on, let\'s re-examine this for a second. Isn\'t this funny? Isn\'t this strange? Isn\'t this a little bit ridiculous?\' That\'s where it is."', '"Funny,Humor,Gamer"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401972', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"The Asian male has an interesting history as far as Western appropriation. At one point, we were completely sexless Chinamen building the railroads. Then, World War II came around, and it was like, Asian guys are coming after the white women. We became a menace for a second."', '"War,History,Women"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401973', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'One of our goals is to figure out ways of diversifying where we are.', '"Goals,Where,Our"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401974', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Venture capitalists don\'t pay attention to you unless you have an app or a widget.', '"Attention,Pay Attention,Pay"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401975', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Content financing is a difficult beast no matter what era of Hollywood we\'re talking about.', '"Beast,Difficult,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401976', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"When we started out doing YouTube videos, I think we were very, very early on in terms of people doing a behind-the-scenes component."', '"YouTube,People,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401977', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"From a creative perspective, we\'ve been very fortunate in that doing it the \'VGHS\' way gave us unlimited freedom. Whatever we wanted to do, however we wanted to do it, we had that."', '"Freedom,Perspective,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401978', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We want to be a studio that makes a whole bunch of stuff we believe in, in all ranges of scale and time and length, and own as much as that IP ourselves and generate as much of that IP ourselves as possible."', '"Time,Believe,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401979', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"If it doesn\'t feel organic to the audience, you gotta trust your gut."', '"Trust,Feel,Organic"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401980', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'A better quality of video is better for everyone.', '"Quality,Better,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401981', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'We don\'t believe in competition.', '"Believe,Competition"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401982', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"I think some people have a vague idea, but the general public has no clue what the actual behind-the-scenes of filmmaking is and what this profession is."', '"Filmmaking,People,Some People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401983', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"A vlog look is a very specific look, and it\'s basically a phone look."', '"Look,Phone,Basically"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401984', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We\'re able to push the envelope with what we\'re doing, both on a technical and artistic level, which is the most that any filmmaker can ask for."', '"Doing,Push,Level"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401985', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We take a lot of pictures with fans, and when they walk away, their parents say, \'Who was that?\'"', '"Walk,Parents,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401986', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"I think if you make good, interesting content with compelling story lines and good characters, people will tune into the web for as long as you want them to."', '"Good,Long,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401987', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'The consumer is the absolute king in everything you do.', '"King,Everything,Consumer"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401988', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Hollywood is just a bunch of middlemen, people trying to facilitate content transfer between creators and viewers."', '"People,Trying,Transfer"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401989', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'A user who essentially costs YouTube money has very little say. The way to have a say is to concretely support the creators and channels you watch directly by giving them money.', '"Money,Support,YouTube"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401990', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'I want to see more people push what it means to be a web show... because it\'s very difficult to make a living making those types of shows.', '"Difficult,People,See"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401991', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"On the advertising side, view count is not the most important thing. It\'s engagement."', '"View,Important,Advertising"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401992', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"When we think about a great movie, I mean, what do we think about? We think about story, we think about character. And when the visual effects aren\'t perfect, we forgive it."', '"Great,Character,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401993', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"While it\'s easy to sit back and cherry pick bad visual effects and blame the industry for making movies the way they are, you\'re really not seeing the whole picture."', '"Movies,Bad,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401994', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Great visual effects serve story and character and in doing so, are, by their very definition, invisible."', '"Great,Character,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401995', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'I have to credit high school for allowing us to mess around with movie stuff at a time when it was a novelty. Experimenting with that and having a very good group of friends to work with made it a very easy decision that this seemed like something I wanted to do with the rest of my life.', '"Life,Work,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401996', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"When we started doing YouTube, the goal was, hey, let\'s make stuff that we want to see, that entertains us."', '"YouTube,See,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401997', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We have an audience, the ability to fund our own projects, own our own projects, the ability to display our projects unencumbered by any middlemen. That\'s the perfect scenario."', '"Perfect,Own,Ability"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401998', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We firmly believe the future of television is online, and Hulu has recognized the value of quality long-form series."', '"Future,Believe,Quality"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('401999', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'We believe that the future for content-creators such as ourselves lies in being able to source project money from an audience and deliver on those projects in a timely and cost-effective manner.', '"Future,Money,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402000', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'We\'ve always wanted to control the video player for our videos. We really want to evolve how comments on videos work.', '"Work,Control,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402001', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'We always said that directors work their whole lives to get final cut on a movie. We have that. So why would you want to run away from what every other director is sprinting toward their entire careers?', '"Work,Always,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402002', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Drift racing is expensive.', '"Racing,Expensive,Drift"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402003', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"In general, a lot of content creators find that their success is unable to support any sort of organization of scale. It\'s pretty difficult to support even three or four employees."', '"Success,Support,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402004', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'The Lionsgate deal came at an opportune time. It allows us to get our projects financed and create long-form content without needing to be reliant on brand deals or crowdsourcing for external financing.', '"Time,Create,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402005', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Hulu understood how much content costs. By remaining defensive, YouTube is losing various aspects of video - long-form, for example - to other companies."', '"YouTube,Losing,Example"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402006', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'YouTube is the place where people go to consume advertisements willingly. It\'s some capitalist dystopian nightmare.', '"YouTube,People,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402007', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Video content yearns to be free.', '"Free,Content,Video"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402008', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'You have to figure out some way of making money without relying on video ads or people paying to download.', '"Money,Making Money,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402009', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Visual effects have always been a part of this art form. And CG is simply a tool on the filmmaker\'s tool belt to tell a story, but when the end result is bad - maybe it\'s not the tool\'s fault."', '"Art,Result,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402010', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"People always ask us, \'When are you guys gonna do a movie? When are you gonna do a TV show?\' And to me, that feels like such a step backwards from where are."', '"Me,Step,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402011', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We are not frou-frou creative types. We have done both sides of the business and are constantly asking ourselves, \'How are we going to pay for this?\' But the criteria is that it must fit with our world."', '"Business,World,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402012', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"We are video consumers first and foremost, and we hate anything appearing in the videos that isn\'t organic."', '"Hate,Anything,Organic"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402013', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'It\'s hard to sell merchandise off YouTube.', '"YouTube,Hard,Sell"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402014', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"When you have a home and create a brand people believe in and want to support, it makes it easier for you to control merchandise and sell it."', '"Home,Believe,Support"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402015', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'Kickstarter has shifted from funding creative projects to funding products and videogames; the biggest funded are consumer electronics and video game projects.', '"Game,Consumer,Electronics"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402016', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', 'We founded RocketJump for two reasons: to provide quality entertainment and to reach as many different audiences as possible.', '"Quality,Entertainment,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402017', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed2', '"Youku Tudou gives us the reach into China that we\'ve been looking for, and we look forward to sharing even more content with international audiences in the near future."', '"Future,Look,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402018', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I couldn\'t ask for a better life.', '"Life,Better,Ask"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402019', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I honestly didn\'t expect this much attention, but it just keeps happening so I must be doing something right."', '"Doing,Attention,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402020', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I\'ve always been one of the youngest guys on the team. But now I\'m one of the older guys, one of the more experienced guys, and I have to be more of a leader. The guys are looking up to me, asking me questions and looking at me to step up."', '"Me,Step,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402021', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I think everything happens for a reason and all the things that happened to me - good, bad - I\'m glad they did. It\'s made me ready for life, for adulthood."', '"Life,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402022', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"Obviously, everybody has their own expectations of you, but you have to have your own expectations for yourself. For me, I\'m right on track."', '"Me,Yourself,Expectations"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402023', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I mean, I couldn\'t ask for a better life, man."', '"Life,Man,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402024', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I need to go play football. I don\'t care about anything else.', '"Football,Care,dont Care"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402025', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I play a lot of Playstation, and always trying to look pretty for the girls."', '"Look,Trying,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402026', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I don\'t know French at all. I took some lessons when I was younger but all I know are the numbers. I\'ve been told basically everyone in Monaco speaks English because of it being a huge vacation spot so I\'m excited about that. I might not need to learn French after all.', '"Numbers,Know,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402027', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'Nothing has been given to me.', '"Me,Nothing,Been"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402028', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'You can\'t do anything to help your team win when you don\'t play.', '"Win,Help,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402029', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"Obviously, I\'m at the beginning of my career, contrary to what anyone else thinks. I\'m 19 years old. In any other country, everywhere else, you\'re a prospect. And that\'s what I am right now in Europe. I\'m a prospect. I\'m not a seasoned veteran."', '"I Am,Beginning,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402030', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"When I\'m out there on the field, I\'m in a whole different world, you know? It\'s like, I\'m just having so much fun."', '"World,Fun,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402031', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"My mom was always the supplier of soccer balls, and so people were always knocking on my door, and trying to get me out so we could play."', '"Mom,Me,Door"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402032', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'What do I have to cheat for? I\'ve always been playing against people older than me anyways. So what do I have to cheat for?', '"Me,People,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402033', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I wanted to get us a place of our own with a little bit more space. The kitchen is just huge, because my mom... lives there, man, and she loves being in the kitchen."', '"Space,Mom,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402034', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I need to be in a stable environment right now in my career. What I mean by that is a place where I can play and not have too much pressure on me and a place I can develop. Monaco wanted me and did whatever they could to get me so I feel very very good about that.', '"Good,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402035', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'A lot of people have been hyped up to be great but just disappeared. I promised myself I wouldn\'t be one of them.', '"Great,Myself,People"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402036', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'It\'s frustrating at times when you think you\'ve earned a chance to play on the field and you\'re over there sitting on the bench. That\'s not the kind of player I am. I\'m the kind of player who wants to be out there on the field and needs to contribute every minute of every game.', '"Chance,Game,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402037', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'It\'s one of the best leagues in Europe in football. Benfica in my opinion is one of the top 10 biggest clubs in the world.', '"Best,Football,World"', '2023-05-29 12:09:00', '2023-05-29 12:09:00'),
	('402038', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I just want to go in with the right attitude and from Day 1 make a difference.', '"Attitude,Day,Make A Difference"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402039', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"I\'m going to go in and play, because the most important thing is playing on the field and being able to contribute. I really am ready."', '"Important,Go,Ready"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402040', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', 'I don\'t want to be one of those guys where I go there and wait a long time before I become a starter.', '"Time,Long,Wait"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402041', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"When you play soccer, most of the time you got to get the ball moving, but once you get into that attacking third you gotta\' be creative, you gotta\' let your talent take over."', '"Time,Talent,Moving"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402042', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"When you get into the game you\'ve got be thinking, when I get into the attacking third I\'m gonna be freakin\' creative."', '"Thinking,Game,Creative"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402043', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"You can teach all the other stuff, you know. You can teach shooting the ball, you can teach having a good touch... passing and whatnot, but when you get out there on the field, it\'s just a mindset you need to go into the game with."', '"Good,Game,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402044', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed3', '"All I can say is, hey, if you have fun doing what you do, if you have fun playing soccer, the creativity is just going to come as time goes on."', '"Time,Fun,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402045', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"I\'m a romantic, and we romantics are more sensitive to the way people feel. We love more, and we hurt more. When we\'re hurt, we hurt for a long time."', '"Love,Time,Romantic"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402046', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"Wasted Days and Wasted Nights, it\'s about days very wrongly invested in a love affair."', '"Love,Wasted,Days"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402047', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', 'Hopefully I\'ll be the first Mexican-American going into Hillbilly Heaven.', '"Heaven,Be The First,First"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402048', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', 'I\'m one year away from 70 and I\'ve had a good run. I really believe I\'m okay.', '"Good,Believe,Okay"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402049', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', 'I was separated from my wife at the time. A lot of people think I wrote it about prison.', '"Time,Wife,People"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402050', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"Whenever I run into prejudice. I smile and feel sorry for them, and I say to myself, There\'s one more argument for birth control."', '"Smile,Myself,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402051', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"They wanted to start recording rock \'n roll, and thought I had the right voice."', '"Start,Voice,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402052', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"My sister and I were born in San Francisco. When our parents died, we came down here to live with relatives."', '"Parents,Live,Relatives"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402053', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', '"In my mind and in my heart, I feel okay. I cannot complain that I haven\'t lived long enough, but I\'d like to live longer."', '"Heart,Mind,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402054', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed4', 'I was dreaming I was on the Sullivan Show.', '"Show,Dreaming,Sullivan"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402055', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"If an actor is going to be an action hero, do it in a Robert Rodriguez movie, because that guy is going to make you look like a million bucks."', '"Hero,Look,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402056', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"When I was a kid, my pop used to take me to the double feature. He would take me - I had two brothers - and we used to go in the early \'80s and check out these grindhouse movies - a double feature, sometimes a triple feature."', '"Movies,Me,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402057', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"I came from the stage so it was a different kind of acting, or a different arena of acting, and I just loved to do it as a kid. It\'s really gratifying to get to create these different characters and to get to create different voices and to get to wear different clothes."', '"Acting,Create,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402058', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"No, there isn\'t a particular type of genre that I\'m drawn to. I\'m more drawn to the possibility of creating different characters, or being able to go from one genre to the other and to show that I could do it, that I could be good at it."', '"Good,Go,More"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402059', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"I\'m drawn more to quality, and so if the quality is in television, I go in that direction. If it\'s in film, I go in that direction. But I don\'t limit myself or discriminate against any of the mediums."', '"Myself,Quality,Direction"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402060', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', 'I would absolutely recommend for actors to start in the theater because it establishes a foundation in your craft that you can build off of.', '"Foundation,Start,Craft"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402061', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"Personally, I need to learn every word on the page before I go in and audition. I have not mastered the skill of holding pages in my hand and acting with pages in my hand. I find that every time I have to look at the page it takes me completely out of the scene."', '"Time,Look,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402062', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed5', '"Get in theater, really work your craft. Get really, really good so that when people say your name, your name is associated with quality, with integrity."', '"Work,Good,Integrity"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402063', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"Government is the great fiction, through which everybody endeavors to live at the expense of everybody else."', '"Great,Government,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402064', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', 'Everyone wants to live at the expense of the state. They forget that the state wants to live at the expense of everyone.', '"Live,Forget,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402065', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"Life, liberty, and property do not exist because men have made laws. On the contrary, it was the fact that life, liberty, and property existed beforehand that caused men to make laws in the first place."', '"Life,Men,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402066', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"When goods do not cross borders, soldiers will."', '"Will,Soldiers,Cross"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402067', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"In short, is not liberty the freedom of every person to make full use of his faculties, so long as he does not harm other persons while doing so?"', '"Freedom,Long,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402068', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', 'The state is the great fictitious entity by which everyone seeks to live at the expense of everyone else.', '"Great,Live,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402069', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"They will come to learn in the end, at their own expense, that it is better to endure competition for rich customers than to be invested with monopoly over impoverished customers."', '"Competition,Better,Rich"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402070', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', 'Often the masses are plundered and do not know it.', '"Know,Masses,Often"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402071', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"Each of us has a natural right, from God, to defend his person, his liberty, and his property."', '"God,Liberty,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402072', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"Finally, is not liberty the restricting of the law only to its rational sphere of organizing the right of the individual to lawful self-defense; of punishing injustice?"', '"Law,Liberty,Injustice"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402073', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"Is not liberty the destruction of all despotism - including, of course, legal despotism?"', '"Legal,Liberty,Destruction"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402074', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed6', '"And what is liberty, whose very name makes the heart beat faster and shakes the world? Is it not the union of all liberties - liberty of conscience, of education, of association, of the press, of travel, or labor, or trade?"', '"Education,Travel,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402075', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Simplicity is the final achievement. After one has played a vast quantity of notes and more notes, it is simplicity that emerges as the crowning reward of art."', '"Art,Achievement,Simplicity"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402076', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"I wish I could throw off the thoughts which poison my happiness, but I take a kind of pleasure in indulging them."', '"Happiness,Thoughts,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402077', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Sometimes I can only groan, and suffer, and pour out my despair at the piano!"', '"Sometimes,I Can,Despair"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402078', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', 'I shall create a new world for myself.', '"Myself,World,New"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402079', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"As long as I have health and strength, I will gladly work all my days."', '"Work,Health,Strength"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402080', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Man is never always happy, and very often only a brief period of happiness is granted him in this world; so why escape from this dream which cannot last long?"', '"Happiness,Man,World"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402081', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Vienna is a handsome, lively city, and pleases me exceedingly."', '"Me,Handsome,City"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402082', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Oh, how hard it must be to die anywhere but in one\'s birthplace."', '"Die,Hard,Birthplace"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402083', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"The crowd intimidates me, its breath suffocates me. I feel paralyzed by its curious look, and the unknown faces make me dumb."', '"Look,Me,Dumb"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402084', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"Oh, how miserable it is to have no one to share your sorrows and joys, and, when your heart is heavy, to have no soul to whom you can pour out your woes."', '"Heart,Soul,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402085', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed7', '"If the newspapers cut me up so much that I shall not venture before the world again, I have resolved to become a house painter; that would be as easy as anything else, and I should, at any rate, still be an artist!"', '"Me,World,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402086', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed8', 'Astronomers sometimes observe that a star of medium magnitude increases suddenly in size; a star invisible to the naked eye may become very brilliant and visible without any telescope - the appearance of a Nova.', '"Sometimes,Naked,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402087', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed8', '"In England and the United States, where physicists have at their disposal equipment of very high voltages, several new elements were prepared using protons and deuterons as projectiles."', '"New,High,Equipment"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402088', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed8', 'The first unquestionable proofs of the transformation of elements into different chemical elements have been provided by the study of the phenomena of radioactivity.', '"Transformation,First,Chemical"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402089', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed8', '"There is no doubt that radium is transformed spontaneously into an active gas, radon, emitting at the same time alpha particles, or helions."', '"Time,Doubt,Active"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402090', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed9', '"The television critic, whatever his pretensions, does not labour in the same vineyard as those he criticizes; his grapes are all sour."', '"Television,Whatever,Grapes"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402091', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fed9', '"As Oscar Wilde should have said, when bad ideas have nowhere else to go, they emigrate to America and become university courses."', '"America,Bad,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402092', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"No man can pass into eternity, for he is already in it."', '"Man,Eternity,He"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402093', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"Man\'s liberty ends, and it ought to end, when that liberty becomes the curse of its neighbors."', '"Man,Liberty,End"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402094', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"There is only one real failure in life that is possible, and that is, not to be true to the best one knows."', '"Life,Best,Failure"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402095', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"Whether the prayer of Seneca was granted we do not know; but, as we do not again hear of Marcus, it is probable that he died before his father, and that the line of Seneca, like that of so many great men, became extinct in the second generation."', '"Men,Great,Prayer"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402096', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"There was living in the palace at this time a brother of the great Germanicus, and consequently an uncle of the late emperor, whose name was Claudius Caesar."', '"Time,Great,Late"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402097', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', 'The decision of such judges as Claudius and his Senate is worth very little in the question of a man\'s innocence or guilt; but the sentence was that Seneca should be banished to the island of Corsica.', '"Man,Decision,Innocence"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402098', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', 'Seneca brings vividly before us a picture of the various scholars assembled in a school of the philosophers.', '"Picture,School,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402099', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"If ever I want to amuse myself with an idiot, I have not far to look for one. I laugh at myself."', '"Myself,Look,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402100', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', '"For although Claudius had been accused of gambling and drunkenness, not only were no worse sins laid to his charge, but he had successfully established some claim to being considered a learned man."', '"Man,Gambling,Worse"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402101', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feda', 'But in the life of every man there are influences of a far more real and penetrating character than those which come through the medium of schools or teachers.', '"Life,Character,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402102', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"God is not looking for repayment, but repentance. What heals a broken relationship is sincere love and contrition."', '"Love,God,Relationship"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402103', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"What\'s wrong with us isn\'t a rap sheet of bad deeds, but a damaged heart, a soul-sickness, that plunges us into fearful self-protection, alienation from God and others."', '"God,Heart,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402104', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"People just don\'t realize how much peer pressure, the desire for peer acclamation, influences them."', '"Pressure,People,Desire"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402105', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Easter may seem boring to children, and it is blessedly unencumbered by the silly fun that plagues Christmas. Yet it contains the one thing needful for every human life: the good news of Resurrection."', '"Life,Good,Christmas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402106', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Of the seven deadly sins, anger has long been the one with the best box of costumes. When the guy in the next car rages at you, he\'s dangerous. When you rage at him, you\'re just. We can usually recognize the results of anger, especially in others, as destructive and evil."', '"Best,Car,Anger"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402107', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'I think intellectualizing annoys me because it is the enemy of experience; you cannot experience the presence of God and analyze it at the same time. You can\'t analyze anything and experience it simultaneously.', '"God,Experience,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402108', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"The Church\'s teaching isn\'t an official statement, but the cumulative understanding of all the people who have loved and experienced Jesus through time."', '"Time,People,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402109', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"The Church is the safe place to be. I can safely believe everything the Church teaches. It will not harm me, and in fact it will equip me to grow and grow and have a better and better ability to experience that direct presence."', '"Experience,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402110', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Jesus showed us how to be courageous and sacrificial while we die for our beliefs, not while we kill for them."', '"Die,Us,Beliefs"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402111', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"My mother was an unbeliever - and still is. My father was a nominal Catholic. We would go in to church at the last minute before the gospel reading, take Communion, and walk right out again."', '"Walk,Father,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402112', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"I was raised in a nominal Roman Catholic home, but without any really strong faith there."', '"Faith,Home,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402113', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"After I graduated from college, while traveling around Europe, hitchhiking, doing the tourist thing, I went into a church in Dublin."', '"Church,Doing,Europe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402114', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"As a teenager and a student, I totally cast away the Christian faith. I just believed it was stupid, and only stupid people could believe it. I actually became an anti-Christian, and very antagonistic."', '"Faith,Stupid,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402115', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"People don\'t do theology in a vacuum but in a community with other theological thinkers, where there\'s jealousy, vanity, hurt pride, all those things."', '"Jealousy,Pride,Community"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402116', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'The Christmas story has such power and such appeal every year. There are other stories we get tired of. You think of your favorite movie; you don\'t want to watch it 15 times.', '"Power,Christmas,Tired"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402117', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Easter tells us of something children can\'t understand, because it addresses things they don\'t yet have to know: the weariness of life, the pain, the profound loneliness and hovering fear of meaninglessness."', '"Life,Fear,Easter"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402118', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"You can latch onto theological ideas that are, in fact, not accurate, and refuse to let them go. I think we\'ve seen this a few times in church history."', '"History,Church,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402119', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'I know by experience that Jesus Christ is a very powerful spirit - I know by experience that he is probably the most powerful spirit in the universe. I know by experience he is not a mere human being. He is something beyond that.', '"Experience,Universe,Jesus Christ"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402120', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'The Orthodox hierarchy doesn\'t have the kind of power that high-ranking clergy do in other churches. There isn\'t even a worldwide governing board to hold all the various Orthodox bodies together.', '"Power,Together,Hold"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402121', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'Someone who wanted to challenge Orthodoxy would not be able to locate a building to hold a protest march in front of. The faith is too diffused.', '"Faith,Building,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402122', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', 'Lots of Orthodox go to church every Sunday but don\'t know much about the faith. Yet they know that there is something that they don\'t know much about.', '"Faith,Church,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402123', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"I\'ve been able to dig deeper into awareness of my own sinfulness, and take baby steps toward spiritual healing. I\'m able to worship in an ancient communion full of awesome beauty, one that is now being blessed with quiet revival."', '"Beauty,Awareness,Blessed"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402124', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"The New Testament Scriptures are full of references to the malice of the devil, but we generally overlook them. I think this is because our idea of salvation is that Christ died on the cross to pay His Father the debt for our sins."', '"Devil,Father,New"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402125', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Temptation coaxes us toward sin, and sin leads to sickness and death, and ultimately confinement in the realm of the evil one."', '"Death,Sickness,Evil"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402126', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"The devil\'s main purpose is not to scare us, in a horror-movie way; when we\'re scared of him, we\'re alert to him, and that might undermine his plans. Instead, he wants to quietly, subtly lure us into stepping away from God."', '"God,Devil,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402127', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"There are lots of things to like about being Eastern Orthodox - incense, liturgies, all the baklava you can eat - but you know what I like best? None of that stupid \'women\'s ministry\' stuff."', '"Best,Women,Stupid"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402128', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Women and men just aren\'t that different. Oh, we\'re different in some intriguing ways, and it can be fun to band together for all-gal or all-guy projects. But when it comes to the tragic mess Christ came to heal, we\'re pretty much the same."', '"Women,Men,Together"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402129', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Women don\'t need to have our own little corner of the church where we can feel precious or, alternatively, cranky. In every essential thing, as far as life in Christ is concerned, the differences between men and women are irrelevant."', '"Life,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402130', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"A segregated spiritual subculture does women no good, even if it does have adorable butterflies in the logo."', '"Women,Good,Spiritual"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402131', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"It is tragic that some Christians have been so battered with stories of a prideful, vindictive God that they have fled from Jesus\' fold."', '"God,Vindictive,Some"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402132', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"God\'s presence is not just Light, and Life, but Love. And Love invites, but does not compel."', '"Life,Love,God"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402133', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"The Bible, that powerful book, has many effects: it comforts, counsels, instructs, and brings us into the presence of God. But trying to erase offense as one of its functions is a fundamentally misguided task."', '"God,Bible,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402134', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedb', '"Somehow we just don\'t make the same boisterous fun of Holy Week that we do of Christmas. No one plans to have a holly, jolly Easter."', '"Christmas,Easter,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402135', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', 'Insulin is not a cure for diabetes; it is a treatment. It enables the diabetic to burn sufficient carbohydrates so that proteins and fats may be added to the diet in sufficient quantities to provide energy for the economic burdens of life.', '"Life,Diet,Energy"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402136', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"I had been taught that if I cried, to be quiet about it, so whereas I never howled, the least thing made me cry both at school and at home. Crying tends to separate a child from other children, for even children dislike a cry baby, and I had no friends in the world."', '"Home,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402137', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"I lived in constant terror of being asked a question in class. Even if I knew the answer, I was never able to tell it before the class."', '"Never,Tell,Answer"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402138', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Best and I worked in the sub-basement of the old medical building day and night. Time, meals, sleep - all were of secondary consideration. We had to get insulin into a form that was refined enough for continued clinical use."', '"Best,Time,Medical"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402139', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', 'It was an extremely trying time for me. Best was still intimate with MacLeod and the others about the laboratory. I was out of the picture entirely. MacLeod had taken over the whole physiological investigation. Collip had taken over the biochemistry. Professor Graham and Dr. Campbell had taken over the whole clinical aspect of the investigation.', '"Best,Time,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402140', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Diabetes mellitus is due to a deficiency of the internal secretion of the pancreas. The main principle of treatment is, therefore, to correct this deficiency."', '"Diabetes,Treatment,Principle"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402141', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"It was because of Henderson that I stayed... It was he and he alone who kept me in Toronto and in Canada. Were it not for Henderson, I believe insulin would have been a product of the United States."', '"Alone,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402142', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"On February 19th, Dr. Collip found that he was unable to refine the extract by his method and was unable to keep up his supply to the wards. During the following six weeks, or longer, no extract was available for clinical tests. I believe the reason for this to be that Collip, wishing to keep his process a secret, had not kept careful records."', '"Believe,Process,Secret"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402143', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Father was very sympathetic, and if the hero of a romance was good or to be pitied, his eyes would fill with tears until he could not see."', '"Good,Eyes,Hero"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402144', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"During the first couple of years at school... I used to take my lunch and go down by the old fair grounds & sit alone by the side of the road & eat it... Those lovely, lonely lunches stick deep in my memory as unhappy times."', '"Alone,Lunch,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402145', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"In the U.S., the incidence of diabetes has increased proportionately with the per capita consumption of sugar."', '"Diabetes,Sugar,Consumption"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402146', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"In the past, war was confined for the most part to men in uniform, but with increased mechanization of armies and the introduction of air forces, there is an increased dependence on the home country, and eight to ten people working at home are now required to keep one man in the fighting line."', '"War,Men,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402147', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Professor Macleod, in his remarks, gave everything that I was going to say and used the pronoun \'we\' throughout. The following day, students were talking about the remarkable work of Professor Macleod."', '"Work,Day,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402148', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Best said possibly the only thing that would have changed my attitude: \'What will happen to me?\' \'Your friend MacLeod will look after you,\' I said. Best replied, \'If you get out, I get out.\' There was silence for some moments. I thought of all the joy of the early experiments which we had known together. Here was loyalty."', '"Attitude,Best,Loyalty"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402149', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', 'I very deeply appreciate the honour which you have conferred upon me in awarding the Nobel Prize for 1923 to me and Professor J.J.R. Macleod.', '"Me,Appreciate,Prize"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402150', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"The place where we were operating was not fit to be called an operating room. Aseptic work had not been done in it for some years. The floor could not be scrubbed properly, or the water would go through on the laboratories below."', '"Work,Water,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402151', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"When I go in, I find that it is not a lab but an office. There are a pile of letters to answer, phone numbers to call up, people waiting to have an interview, routine work that must be done."', '"Work,Waiting,People"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402152', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', 'The method of estimating the potency of insulin solutions is based on the effect that insulin produces upon the blood sugar of normal animals.', '"Sugar,Blood,Normal"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402153', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"If a patient became sugar-free and blood sugar normal on a basal requirement diet, the caloric intake was gradually increased until sugar appeared in the urine. The tolerance was thus ascertained."', '"Diet,Tolerance,Sugar"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402154', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"My work is entirely surgical, and Col. Starr has given me a very interesting task of collecting nerve cases that have had the nerves sewn together. I may also do some experimental work for him."', '"Work,Together,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402155', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"I looked at one little print for a long time. It was called \'The Landing.\' It showed men tugging on a rope, pulling a boat up onto skids out of the water. The thought occurred to me that I might paint such a picture."', '"Time,Men,Water"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402156', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', 'British Forces should be in a position to give back in a ten fold measure any attack that the Germans may attempt.', '"Back,Position,Attack"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402157', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Especially during the hot weather, we have been so greatly hampered by infections despite our utmost care, and since we have lost so many dogs, I strongly desire more help to keep the place clean and gloves and gowns and a thorough fitting up of our operating room."', '"Weather,Hot,Care"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402158', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Mr. Best has expressed the desire to work with me, and I should be more than pleased to have him. His work has been excellent, and he is absolutely honest, careful, and impartial and has taken a great interest in the work."', '"Work,Best,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402159', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedc', '"Henderson had a thousand times more to do with the discovery of insulin than had Macleod. In the first place, he knew more about it. In the second place, he was consulted before every series of experiments, and he advised, criticized, or commended."', '"Place,Discovery,Second Place"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402160', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', '"If it seems a childish thing to do, do it in remembrance that you are a child."', '"Childish,Child,Remembrance"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402161', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', '"Pay mind to your own life, your own health, and wholeness. A bleeding heart is of no help to anyone if it bleeds to death."', '"Life,Health,Death"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402162', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', 'Compassion is sometimes the fatal capacity for feeling what it is like to live inside somebody else\'s skin. It is the knowledge that there can never really be any peace and joy for me until there is peace and joy finally for you too.', '"Knowledge,Peace,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402163', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', '"In his holy flirtation with the world, God occasionally drops a handkerchief. These handkerchiefs are called saints."', '"God,World,Drops"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402164', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', '"The grace of God means something like: Here is your life. You might never have been, but you are because the party wouldn\'t have been complete without you."', '"Life,God,Grace"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402165', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', 'Religion points to that area of human experience where in one way or another man comes upon mystery as a summons to pilgrimage.', '"Experience,Religion,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402166', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', 'It is as impossible for man to demonstrate the existence of God as it would be for even Sherlock Holmes to demonstrate the existence of Arthur Conan Doyle.', '"God,Man,Impossible"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402167', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedd', 'You can\'t be too careful what you tell a child because you never know what he\'ll take hold of and spend the rest of his life remembering you by.', '"Life,Rest,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402168', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fede', 'Take a look at your natural river. What are you? Stop playing games with yourself. Where\'s your river going? Are you riding with it? Or are you rowing against it? Don\'t you see that there is no effort if you\'re riding with your river?', '"Look,River,Effort"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402169', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fede', 'The key to your universe is that you can choose.', '"Universe,Your,Choose"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402170', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fede', 'Knowing where you\'re going is all you need to get there.', '"Knowing,Need,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402171', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fede', 'Your range of available choices - right now - is limitless.', '"Choices,Right,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402172', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedf', 'Music is an outburst of the soul.', '"Music,Soul,Outburst"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402173', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fedf', '"There is only one real happiness in life, and that is the happiness of creating."', '"Life,Happiness,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402174', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'It is easier to build strong children than to repair broken men.', '"Men,Parenting,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402175', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Where justice is denied, where poverty is enforced, where ignorance prevails, and where any one class is made to feel that society is an organized conspiracy to oppress, rob and degrade them, neither persons nor property will be safe."', '"Society,Justice,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402176', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"It is not light that we need, but fire; it is not the gentle shower, but thunder. We need the storm, the whirlwind, and the earthquake."', '"Nature,Fire,Storm"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402177', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'I prayed for twenty years but received no answer until I prayed with my legs.', '"Religion,Legs,Answer"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402178', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'Power concedes nothing without a demand. It never did and it never will.', '"Power,Nothing,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402179', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'The limits of tyrants are prescribed by the endurance of those whom they oppress.', '"Limits,Endurance,Tyrants"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402180', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'Find out just what any people will quietly submit to and you have the exact measure of the injustice and wrong which will be imposed on them.', '"People,Will,Injustice"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402181', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"The life of the nation is secure only while the nation is honest, truthful, and virtuous."', '"Life,Nation,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402182', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"I am a Republican, a black, dyed in the wool Republican, and I never intend to belong to any other party than the party of freedom and progress."', '"Freedom,Black,Progress"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402183', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"If there is no struggle, there is no progress."', '"Change,Struggle,Progress"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402184', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'No man can put a chain about the ankle of his fellow man without at last finding the other end fastened about his own neck.', '"Man,End,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402185', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'To suppress free speech is a double wrong. It violates the rights of the hearer as well as those of the speaker.', '"Free,Wrong,Speech"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402186', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'One and God make a majority.', '"God,Majority,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402187', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'The thing worse than rebellion is the thing that causes rebellion.', '"Rebellion,Worse,Than"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402188', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'The soul that is within me no man can degrade.', '"Strength,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402189', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"I prefer to be true to myself, even at the hazard of incurring the ridicule of others, rather than to be false, and to incur my own abhorrence."', '"Myself,True,My Own"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402190', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"People might not get all they work for in this world, but they must certainly work for all they get."', '"Work,World,People"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402191', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"America is false to the past, false to the present, and solemnly binds herself to be false to the future."', '"Future,Past,America"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402192', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'I didn\'t know I was a slave until I found out I couldn\'t do the things I wanted.', '"Know,Things,Wanted"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402193', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'The white man\'s happiness cannot be purchased by the black man\'s misery.', '"Happiness,Black,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402194', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'We have to do with the past only as we can make it useful to the present and the future.', '"Future,Past,Present"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402195', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"A man\'s character always takes its hue, more or less, from the form and color of things about him."', '"Character,Man,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402196', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Those who profess to favor freedom, and yet depreciate agitation, are men who want crops without plowing up the ground."', '"Freedom,Men,Ground"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402197', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"A gentleman will not insult me, and no man not a gentleman can insult me."', '"Man,Me,Gentleman"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402198', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"At a time like this, scorching irony, not convincing argument, is needed."', '"Time,Argument,Irony"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402199', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'Man\'s greatness consists in his ability to do and the proper application of his powers to things needed to be done.', '"Man,Greatness,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402200', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'What to the Slave is the 4th of July.', 'July', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402201', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'When men sow the wind it is rational to expect that they will reap the whirlwind.', '"Men,Wind,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402202', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'There is not a man beneath the canopy of Heaven who does not know that slavery is wrong for him.', '"Man,Heaven,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402203', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'I recognize the Republican party as the sheet anchor of the colored man\'s political hopes and the ark of his safety.', '"Political,Man,Safety"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402204', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"A little learning, indeed, may be a dangerous thing, but the want of learning is a calamity to any people."', '"Learning,People,Dangerous"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402205', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Those who profess to favor freedom, and yet deprecate agitation, are men who want crops without plowing up the ground."', '"Freedom,Men,Ground"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402206', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'That which is inhuman cannot be divine.', '"Divine,Cannot,Inhuman"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402207', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"A battle lost or won is easily described, understood, and appreciated, but the moral growth of a great nation requires reflection, as well as observation, to appreciate it."', '"Great,Growth,Reflection"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402208', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Experience demonstrates that there may be a wages of slavery only a little less galling and crushing in its effects than chattel slavery, and that this slavery of wages must go down with the other."', '"Experience,Down,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402209', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', 'Slaves are generally expected to sing as well as to work.', '"Work,Well,Sing"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402210', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Everybody has asked the question, and they learned to ask it early of the abolitionists, \'What shall we do with the Negro?\' I have had but one answer from the beginning. Do nothing with us! Your doing with us has already played the mischief with us."', '"Beginning,Nothing,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402211', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"I could, as a free man, look across the bay toward the Eastern Shore where I was born a slave."', '"Man,Look,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402212', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee0', '"Fugitive slaves were rare then, and as a fugitive slave lecturer, I had the advantage of being the first one out."', '"Rare,First,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402213', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee1', 'The man in gray decided to take the Glen Suite of diamonds at midnight. Provided they were still in the apartment safe and the occupants away. This he needed to know. So he watched and he waited. At half past seven he was rewarded.', '"Man,Past,Safe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402214', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee1', 'The Internet offers authors and their readers a new diversity of opportunities and freedom.', '"Freedom,Internet,Diversity"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402215', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee1', '"In the 66 years that I have been alive, there has not been one hour, of one day, of one month, of one year, when there has not been a threat aimed at us."', '"Day,Alive,One Day"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402216', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee1', 'The British have always coped without becoming a dictatorship.', '"Dictatorship,Always,British"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402217', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee2', '"Every man is his own ancestor, and every man is his own heir. He devises his own future, and he inherits his own past."', '"Future,Man,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402218', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee2', '"And I seemed to discern a power and meaning in the old, which the more impassioned would not allow."', '"Power,Old,Meaning"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402219', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee2', '"Dreaming is an act of pure imagination, attesting in all men a creative power, which if it were available in waking, would make every man a Dante or Shakespeare."', '"Men,Power,Imagination"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402220', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee2', 'No form of Christianity is absolutely and only true.', '"True,Only,Christianity"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402221', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee4', 'Each age tries to form its own conception of the past. Each age writes the history of the past anew with reference to the conditions uppermost in its own time.', '"History,Time,Age"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402222', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee4', '"The existence of an area of free land, its continuous recession, and the advance of American settlement, explain American development."', '"Free,Development,American"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402223', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee4', 'The West is now closed.', '"Now,West,Closed"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402224', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee5', '"The possession of arbitrary power has always, the world over, tended irresistibly to destroy humane sensibility, magnanimity, and truth."', '"Truth,Power,World"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402225', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee5', '"With regard to the moral and religious condition of the slaves, I cannot, either from what I observe, or from what is told me, consider it in any way gratifying."', '"Me,Way,Moral"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402226', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee5', '"This is just what I have thought when I have seen slaves at work - they seem to go through the motions of labor without putting strength into them. They keep their powers in reserve for their own use at night, perhaps."', '"Work,Strength,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402227', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee6', '"Yes, hell exists. It is not a fairy tale. One indeed burns there. This hell is not at the end of life. It is here. At the beginning. Hell is what the infant must experience before he gets to us."', '"Life,Experience,Hell"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402228', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee6', '"This howling mouth, this head which rolls back and tries to escape."', '"Escape,Back,Mouth"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402229', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee6', '"These hands which stretch out, implore, beg, then rise to the head in a gesture of calamity."', '"Rise,Hands,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402230', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee6', '"This tragic brow, these closed eyes, eyebrows raised and knotted."', '"Eyes,Eyebrows,Raised"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402231', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee7', 'Everything is more complicated than it looks to most people.', '"People,Everything,Complicated"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402232', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee7', '"Wilson thought in terms of the whole world; Harding was for America first. And, finally, whereas Wilson wanted America to exert itself nobly, Harding wanted to give it a rest."', '"World,Rest,America"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402233', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee8', '"The world\'s as ugly as sin, and almost as delightful."', '"World,Ugly,Sin"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402234', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee9', '"There is a vast difference - a constitutional difference-between restrictions imposed by the state which prohibit the intellectual commingling of students, and the refusal of individuals to commingle where the state presents no such bar."', '"Difference,Intellectual,State"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402235', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fee9', '"Wars are not acts of God. They are caused by man, by man-made institutions, by the way in which man has organized his society. What man has made, man can change."', '"Change,God,Society"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402236', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feea', '"I would rather write for the instruction, or even the amusement of the poor than for the amusement of the rich."', '"Rich,Poor,Rather"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402237', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feea', 'It\'s just six of one and half-a-dozen of the other.', '"Six,Just,Other"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402238', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'Our lady the Common Law is a very wise old lady though she still has something to learn in telling what she knows.', '"Wise,Law,Lady"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402239', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'Medieval justice was a quaint thing.', '"Justice,Thing,Medieval"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402240', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"Consider the Essay as a political pamphlet on the Revolution side, and the fact that it was the Whig gospel for a century, and you will see its working merit."', '"Political,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402241', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'The practice of the law is a perfectly distinct art.', '"Art,Law,Practice"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402242', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"Not that pleading can be taken as a test, for the forms of action, notably Debt, ignore the fundamental difference between duties imposed by law and duties created by the will of the parties."', '"Action,Law,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402243', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'It is odd how learned persons fail to see that new terms and definitions are apt to mean new doubts and litigation.', '"New,See,Mean"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402244', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'The oldest theory of contract is I think negative.', '"Negative,Contract,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402245', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'Have you ever found any logical reason why mutual promises are sufficient consideration for one another (like the two lean horses of a Calcutta hack who can only just stand together)? I have not.', '"Together,Stand,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402246', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"It cannot be assumed that equity was following common law whenever they agreed, any more than the converse."', '"Law,Equity,More"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402247', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"So far I go with the Socialists as to think it a pretty general rule that, where monopoly is necessary, it is better in public hands."', '"Better,Hands,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402248', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'It is strange how little harm bad codes do.', '"Bad,Strange,Harm"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402249', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'I have not heard that even the New York abortion has done very much in the States where it has been enacted.', '"New,Done,Abortion"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402250', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"If you deny that any principles of conduct at all are common to and admitted by all men who try to behave reasonably - well, I don\'t see how you can have any ethics or any ethical background for law."', '"Men,Law,Ethics"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402251', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'But it is strange how many rational beings believe the ultimate truths of the universe to be reducible to patterns on a blackboard.', '"Believe,Universe,Strange"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402252', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'Yet when one suspects that a man knows something about life that one hasn\'t heard before one is uneasy until one has found out what he has to say.', '"Life,Man,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402253', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', '"Crabbed and obscure definitions are of no use beyond a narrow circle of students, of whom probably every one has a pet one of his own."', '"Pet,Circle,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402254', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feeb', 'The lawyer has not reached the height of his vocation who does not find therein... scope for a peculiar but genuine artistic function.', '"Lawyer,Genuine,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402255', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"In 1958, I was a delegate to the Atoms for Peace conference in Geneva."', '"Peace,Conference,Atoms"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402256', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"My early childhood memories center around this typical American country store and life in a small American town, including 4th of July celebrations marked by fireworks and patriotic music played from a pavilion bandstand."', '"Life,Music,Patriotism"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402257', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"This line of research continued when I went, and brought my research group with me, to the new University of California, Irvine campus in 1966 to become the founding Dean of the School of Physical Sciences."', '"Me,Research,New"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402258', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"During my participation in the Manhattan Project and subsequent research at Los Alamos, encompassing a period of fifteen years, I worked in the company of perhaps the greatest collection of scientific talent the world has ever known."', '"World,Talent,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402259', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"Among my activities was membership in the Boy Scouts; I rose each year through the ranks, eventually achieving the rank of Eagle Scout and undertaking leadership roles in the organization."', '"Leadership,Eagle,Organization"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402260', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"However, I had a chance encounter with an admissions officer of Stevens Institute of Technology, who so impressed me by his erudition and enthusiasm for the school that I changed course and entered Stevens Institute."', '"Technology,Chance,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402261', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', 'I received my undergraduate degree in engineering in 1939 and a Master of Science degree in mathematical physics in 1941 at Steven Institute of Technology.', '"Science,Technology,Graduation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402262', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"I served as Dean until 1974, when I stepped down to return to full time teaching and research."', '"Time,Research,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402263', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', 'I turned my attention for a while to gamma ray astronomy and soon began the first in a continous series of experiments at the Savannah River site to study the properties of the neutrino.', '"River,Attention,Experiments"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402264', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', 'I was strongly encouraged by a science teacher who took an interest in me and presented me with a key to the laboratory to allow me to work whenever I wanted.', '"Work,Science,Teacher"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402265', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', 'In 1956 we observed the electron antineutrino.', '"Electron,Observed"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402266', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"Most of these experiments required the reduction of the cosmic ray muon flux in order to be successful, and the group necessarily became expert in the operation of deep underground laboratories."', '"Group,Expert,Experiments"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402267', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"Our home had many books due principally to the educational interests of my sister and two brothers, all of whom where serious students engaged in professional studies; my sister became a doctor of medicine and my brothers became lawyers."', '"Home,Doctor,Medicine"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402268', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feec', '"Over the years, a number of other intriguing experimental ideas and areas of investigation have been the objects of my attention, and I have devoted some time and effort to exploring the inherent possbilities."', '"Time,Effort,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402269', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'Scientific research is one of the most exciting and rewarding of occupations.', '"Science,Research,Exciting"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402270', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"It is like a voyage of discovery into unknown lands, seeking not for new territory but for new knowledge. It should appeal to those with a good sense of adventure."', '"Knowledge,Good,New"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402271', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'I was married to Margaret Joan Howe in 1940. Although not a scientist herself she has contributed more to my work than anyone else by providing a peaceful and happy home.', '"Work,Home,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402272', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'Through art and science in their broadest senses it is possible to make a permanent contribution towards the improvement and enrichment of human life and it is these pursuits that we students are engaged in.', '"Life,Science,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402273', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'I and my colleagues here have been engaged in the pursuit of knowledge.', '"Knowledge,Colleagues,Here"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402274', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"And indeed this theme has been at the centre of all my research since 1943, both because of its intrinsic fascination and my conviction that a knowledge of sequences could contribute much to our understanding of living matter."', '"Knowledge,Research,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402275', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"I believe that we have been doing this not primarily to achieve riches or even honour, but rather because we were interested in the work, enjoyed doing it and felt very strongly that it was worthwhile."', '"Work,Believe,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402276', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"Influenced by him, and probably even more so by my brother Theodore (a year older than me), I soon became interested in biology and developed a respect for the importance of science and the scientific method."', '"Science,Respect,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402277', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"Initially I had intended to study medicine, but before going to University I had decided that I would be better suited to a career in which I could concentrate my activities and interests more on a single goal than appeared to be possible in my father\'s profession."', '"Father,Better,Medicine"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402278', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"After taking my B.A. degree in 1939 I remained at the University for a further year to take an advanced course in Biochemistry, and surprised myself and my teachers by obtaining a first class examination result."', '"Myself,Result,Degree"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402279', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', '"It was Neuberger who first taught me how to do research, both technically and as a way of life, and I owe much to him."', '"Life,Me,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402280', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'Until 1943 I received no stipend. I was able to support myself as my mother was the daughter of a relatively wealthy cotton manufacturer.', '"Myself,Support,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402281', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'In this atmosphere I soon became interested in nucleic acids.', '"Atmosphere,Soon,Interested"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402282', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feed', 'When I was young my Father used to tell me that the two most worthwhile pursuits in life were the pursuit of truth and of beauty and I believe that Alfred Nobel must have felt much the same when he gave these prizes for literature and the sciences.', '"Life,Beauty,Truth"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402283', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feee', '"Men who are engaged in public life must necessarily aim at reducing opposition to a minimum, and one of the most obvious means to that end is by misrepresenting, discrediting or ruining their opponents."', '"Life,Men,Aim"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402284', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feee', '"It is true that the politician, in his professional character, does not always, or even very often, conform to the most approved pattern of private conduct."', '"Character,True,Politician"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402285', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feee', '"No politician has ever yet been able to rule his country, nor has any country ever yet been able to face the world, upon the principles of the Sermon on the Mount."', '"Face,World,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402286', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'There is nothing left now for us but to get ever deeper and deeper into debt to the banking system in order to provide the increasing amounts of money the nation requires for its expansion and growth.', '"Money,Growth,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402287', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"Now whatever the origin of this apparently meaningless jumble of ideas may have been, it is really a perfect and very slightly allegorical expression of the actual present views we hold today."', '"Today,Perfect,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402288', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"Chemistry has been termed by the physicist as the messy part of physics, but that is no reason why the physicists should be permitted to make a mess of chemistry when they invade it."', '"Physics,Chemistry,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402289', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'An honest money system is the only alternative.', '"Money,Only,System"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402290', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'But what sin is to the moralist and crime to the jurist so to the scientific man is ignorance.', '"Man,Ignorance,Sin"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402291', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"In the first place, the preparation of the Nobel lecture which I am to give has shown me, even more clearly than I knew before, how many others share with me, often, indeed, have anticipated me, in the discoveries for which you have awarded me the prize."', '"Me,I Am,Preparation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402292', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"It is curious to reflect, for example, upon the remarkable legend of the Philosopher\'s Stone, one of the oldest and most universal beliefs, the origin of which, however far back we penetrate into the records of the past, we do not probably trace its real source."', '"Legend,Past,Stone"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402293', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'Man cannot influence in this respect the atomic forces of Nature.', '"Nature,Respect,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402294', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"Nature is in austere mood, even terrifying, withal majestically beautiful."', '"Nature,Beautiful,Mood"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402295', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'On our plane knowledge and ignorance are the immemorial adversaries.', '"Knowledge,Ignorance,Our"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402296', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'Scientific men can hardly escape the charge of ignorance with regard to the precise effect of the impact of modern science upon the mode of living of the people and upon their civilisation.', '"Science,Men,Ignorance"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402297', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"The pure air and dazzling snow belong to things beyond the reach of all personal feeling, almost beyond the reach of life. Yet such things are a part of our life, neither the least noble nor the most terrible."', '"Life,Air,Pure"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402298', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'The whole profit of the issuance of money has provided the capital of the great banking business as it exists today.', '"Business,Money,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402299', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'There is something sublime about its aloofness from and its indifference to its external environment.', '"Environment,Something,About"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402300', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', '"To-day it appears as though it may well be altogether abolished in the future as it has to some extent been mitigated in the past by the unceasing, and as it now appears, unlimited ascent of man to knowledge, and through knowledge to physical power and dominion over Nature."', '"Nature,Knowledge,Future"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402301', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feef', 'With all our mastery over the powers of Nature we have adhered to the view that the struggle for existence is a permanent and necessary condition of life.', '"Life,Nature,Struggle"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402302', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef0', '"Softly the loud peal dies, In passing winds it drowns, But breathes, like perfect joys, Tender tones."', '"Perfect,Like,Loud"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402303', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef0', '"What would it profit thee to be the first Of echoes, tho thy tongue should live forever, A thing that answers, but hath not a thought As lasting but as senseless as a stone."', '"Stone,Live,Forever"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402304', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'He who defends everything defends nothing.', '"Brainy,Nothing,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402305', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'A crown is merely a hat that lets the rain in.', '"Power,Rain,Hat"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402306', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'Every man has a wild beast within him.', '"Man,Beast,Wild"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402307', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'An educated people can be easily governed.', '"Education,People,Educated"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402308', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', '"If my soldiers were to begin to think, not one of them would remain in the army."', '"Army,Think,Begin"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402309', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', '"The greatest and noblest pleasure which we have in this world is to discover new truths, and the next is to shake off old prejudices."', '"World,New,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402310', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', '"Rogues, would you live forever?"', '"Live,Forever,Would"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402311', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'Religion is the idol of the mob; it adores everything it does not understand.', '"Religion,Everything,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402312', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', '"My people and I have come to an agreement which satisfied us both. They are to say what they please, and I am to do what I please."', '"I Am,People,Satisfied"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402313', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'I begin by taking. I shall find scholars later to demonstrate my perfect right.', '"Perfect,Find,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402314', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', '"Don\'t forget your great guns, which are the most respectable arguments of the rights of kings."', '"Great,Forget,Kings"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402315', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'What is the good of experience if you do not reflect?', '"Experience,Good,Reflect"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402316', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef8', 'It seems to me that man is made to act rather than to know: the principles of things escape our most persevering researches.', '"Man,Me,Escape"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402317', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'A manager is not a person who can do the work better than his men; he is a person who can get his men to do the work better than he can.', '"Work,Men,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402318', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'Information about the package is as important as the package itself.', '"Information,Important,Package"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402319', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'Fear of failure must never be a reason not to try something.', '"Failure,Fear,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402320', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"Leadership is simply the ability of an individual to coalesce the efforts of other individuals toward achieving common goals. It boils down to looking after your people and ensuring that, from top to bottom, everyone feels part of the team."', '"Leadership,Goals,Looking"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402321', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"A Yale University management professor in response to student Fred Smith\'s paper proposing reliable overnight delivery service: The concept is interesting and well-formed, but in order to earn better than a \'C\', the idea must be feasible."', '"Service,Better,Management"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402322', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'Leaders get out in front and stay there by raising the standards by which they judge themselves - and by which they are willing to be judged.', '"Judge,Stay,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402323', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'I\'m not afraid to take a swing and miss.', '"Swing,Afraid,Miss"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402324', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"There is no free market for oil. It\'s controlled by a cartel, OPEC."', '"Free,Oil,Market"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402325', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"If you look historically, what creates growth and wealth is innovation and investment, and increase in scale - more customers."', '"Growth,Look,Wealth"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402326', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"The biggest part of our business has always been moving things, not paper. With the Internet, people in Mississippi can buy things from Macedonia, without regard to time or place or quantity."', '"Business,Time,Internet"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402327', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'I do not believe I could have built FedEx without the skills I learned from the Marine Corps.', '"Believe,Skills,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402328', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"Every time we make an investment decision at FedEx, we ask ourselves: \'What is the return on this investment?\'"', '"Time,Decision,Investment"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402329', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'Only electricity can give the transport sector the flexibility to switch fuels when one or more become too expensive.', '"Electricity,More,Expensive"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402330', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"My innovation involved taking an idea from the telecommunications and banking industries, and applying that idea to transportation business."', '"Business,Innovation,Transportation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402331', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'I am not someone who tends to advocate for increased government involvement in the private sector.', '"Government,I Am,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402332', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"The tax rate of 35 percent is impossible to provide an incentive to the large corporations, that have $1.7 trillion offshore, to put their money back in the United States."', '"Money,Impossible,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402333', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'My four years in the Marine Corps left me with an indelible understanding of the value of leadership skills.', '"Leadership,Me,Value"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402334', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"The United States tax system today is very prejudiced towards financialization, leverage, and lack of investment."', '"Today,Investment,System"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402335', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', '"Beginning in 1973 and then acts in \'77, \'78, 1980, 1994 and then into the 21st century in the international arena, governments have steadily gotten out of the transportation business."', '"Business,Beginning,Transportation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402336', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef2', 'A lot of the economy is indeed being supplied by goods that are produced offshore. And much of the reason for that is societal.', '"Reason,Indeed,Economy"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402337', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef3', 'Hardly a competent workman can be found who does not devote a considerable amount of time to studying just how slowly he can work and still convince his employer that he is going at a good pace.', '"Work,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402338', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef3', 'In the past the man has been first; in the future the system must be first... The first object of any good system must be that of developing first class men.', '"Future,Good,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402339', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef4', 'The rumor that the state of my health will necessitate my resignation is entirely unfounded.', '"Health,Will,Resignation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402340', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef4', '"I have no intention of resigning, and confidently expect to resume official duties within three months."', '"Three,Intention,Resume"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402341', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef4', '"My recovery, though slower than hoped for, is nevertheless assured."', '"Nevertheless,Though,Recovery"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402342', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', 'Every moment of resistance to temptation is a victory.', '"Moment,Victory,Temptation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402343', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"Kind words are the music of the world. They have a power which seems to be beyond natural causes, as if they were some angel\'s song, which had lost its way and come on Earth, and sang on undyingly, smiting the hearts of men with sweetest wounds, and putting for the while an angel\'s nature into us."', '"Nature,Men,Power"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402344', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"Kindness has converted more sinners than zeal, eloquence, or learning."', '"Learning,Kindness,More"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402345', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"Many a friendship, long, loyal, and self-sacrificing, rested at first on no thicker a foundation than a kind word."', '"Friendship,Long,Foundation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402346', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', 'They always win who side with God.', '"God,Win,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402347', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"Kind words produce happiness. How often have we ourselves been made happy by kind words, in a manner and to an extent which we are unable to explain!"', '"Happiness,Words,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402348', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"Happiness is a great power of holiness. Thus, kind words, by their power of producing happiness, have also a power of producing holiness, and so of winning men to God."', '"Happiness,God,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402349', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', 'The buried talent is the sunken rock on which most lives strike and founder.', '"Talent,Rock,Founder"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402350', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', 'Kind thoughts are rarer than either kind words or deeds. They imply a great deal of thinking about others. This in itself is rare. But they also imply a great deal of thinking about others without the thoughts being criticisms. This is rarer still.', '"Great,Thoughts,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402351', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"If I may use such a word when I am speaking of religious subjects, it is by voice and words that men \'mesmerize\' each other. Hence it is that the world is converted by the voice of the preacher."', '"Men,World,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402352', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef5', '"It has always seemed to me that a love of natural objects, and the depth, as well as exuberance and refinement of mind, produced by an intelligent delight in scenery, are elements of the first importance in the education of the young."', '"Love,Education,Scenery"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402353', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', '"Whether you\'re a newspaper journalist, a lawyer, a doctor. You have to organize your thoughts."', '"Doctor,Thoughts,Lawyer"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402354', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', 'Anybody whose mind is functioning at all can\'t be content with the way the world works.', '"World,Mind,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402355', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', 'My goal is to make as many films as possible about different aspects of American life.', '"Life,American,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402356', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', '"You have to edit the material. That assumes that some kind of a mind is operating in relation to the material. Not all minds are the same. Every aspect of filmmaking requires choice. The selection of the subject, the shooting, editing and length are all aspects of choice."', '"Editing,Mind,Filmmaking"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402357', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', 'I don\'t like to read novels where the novelist tells me what to think about the situation and the characters. I prefer to discover for myself.', '"Myself,Me,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402358', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fef7', '"I hope that not only my documentaries, but everybody\'s documentaries, last. It will really confuse historians in the next century, because they\'ll have, in addition to all the print material, they\'ll have all these pictures to look at."', '"Hope,Look,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402359', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"My first thought was always a cigarette. It still is, but I haven\'t cheated."', '"Always,First,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402360', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', 'I\'m pretty catholic about what constitutes science fiction.', '"Science,Science Fiction,Pretty"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402361', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"You look at the world around you, and you take it apart into all its components. Then you take some of those components, throw them away, and plug in different ones, start it up and see what happens."', '"Look,World,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402362', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"If you don\'t care about science enough to be interested in it on its own, you shouldn\'t try to write hard science fiction. You can write like Ray Bradbury and Harlan Ellison as much as you want."', '"Science,Care,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402363', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"People ask me how I do research for my science fiction. The answer is, I never do any research."', '"Science,Me,Research"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402364', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"Stories where the author has known very little, but run a computer program that tells him how to construct a planet, and looked up specific things about rocketry and so on, really suck."', '"Things,Up,About"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402365', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"I don\'t think the scientific method and the science fictional method are really analogous. The thing about them is that neither is really practiced very much, at least not consciously. But the fact that they are methodical does relate them."', '"Science,Think,About"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402366', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"I\'m doing a book, \'Chasing Science,\' about the pleasures of science as a spectator sport."', '"Science,Doing,Pleasures"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402367', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', 'It\'s clear that science and science fiction have overlapping populations.', '"Science,Science Fiction,Clear"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402368', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"Stephen Hawking said he spent most of his first couple of years at Cambridge reading science fiction (and I believe that, because his grades weren\'t all that great)."', '"Science,Great,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402369', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', 'A lot of the cosmologists and astrophysicists clearly had been reading science fiction.', '"Science,Science Fiction,Reading"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402370', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', 'The head of Fermilab was reading Astonishing Stories when he was ten.', '"Head,Reading,He"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402371', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"A large fraction of the most interesting scientists have read a lot of SF at one time or another, either early enough that it may have played a part in their becoming scientists or at some later date just because they liked the ideas."', '"Time,Ideas,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402372', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"My old English buddy, John Rackham, wrote and told me what made science fiction different from all other kinds of literature - science fiction is written according to the science fiction method."', '"Science,Me,Literature"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402373', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', 'The science fiction method is dissection and reconstruction.', '"Science,Science Fiction,Fiction"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402374', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"That\'s the method: restructure the world we live in in some way, then see what happens."', '"World,Way,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402375', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"In terms of stories I would buy for a science fiction magazine, if they take place in the future, that might do it."', '"Science,Future,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402376', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"I was thinking of writing a little foreword saying that history is, after all, based on people\'s recollections, which change with time."', '"Change,History,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402377', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"The big new development in my life is, when I turned 80, I decided I no longer have to do four pages a day. For me, it\'s like retiring."', '"Life,Me,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402378', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefa', '"I did that for 40 years or more. I never had any writer\'s block. I got up in the morning, sat down at the typewriter - now, computer - lit up a cigarette."', '"Morning,Never,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402379', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"The standardization of world culture, with local popular or traditional forms driven out or dumbed down to make way for American television, American music, food, clothes and films, has been seen by many as the very heart of globalization."', '"Food,Music,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402380', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"And this fear that US models are replacing everything else now spills over from the sphere of culture into our two remaining categories: for this process is clearly, at one level, the result of economic domination - of local cultural industries closed down by American rivals."', '"Fear,Culture,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402381', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"The United States has made a massive effort since the end of the Second World War to secure the dominance of its films in foreign markets - an achievement generally pushed home politically, by writing clauses into various treaties and aid packages."', '"War,Home,World"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402382', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"So is it always nationalist to resist US globalization? The US thinks it is, and wants you to agree; and, moreover, to consider US interests as being universal ones."', '"Globalization,Always,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402383', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"Often, these downplay the power of cultural imperialism - in that sense, playing the game of US interests - by reassuring us that the global success of American mass culture is not as bad as all that."', '"Success,Power,Culture"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402384', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', 'In most of the European countries - France stands out in its resistance to this particular form of American cultural imperialism - the national film industries were forced onto the defensive after the war by such binding agreements.', '"War,American,Film"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402385', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"If it is, in reality, capitalism that is the motor force behind the destructive forms of globalization, then it must be in their capacity to neutralize or transform this particular mode of exploitation that one can best test these various forms of resistance to the West."', '"Best,Reality,Globalization"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402386', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', 'The more worrying feature of the new global corporate structures is their capacity to devastate national labour markets by transferring their operations to cheaper locations overseas.', '"New,More,Operations"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402387', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"For when we talk about the spreading power and influence of globalization, aren\'t we really referring to the spreading economic and military might of the US?"', '"Power,Globalization,Influence"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402388', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefc', '"A further point is that, little by little, in the current universe, everything is slowly being named; nor does this have anything to do with the older Aristotelian universals in which the idea of a chair subsumes all its individual manifestations."', '"Universe,Chair,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402389', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefd', 'Keep interested in others; keep interested in the wide and wonderful world. Then in a spiritual sense you will always be young.', '"World,Spiritual,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402390', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefd', '"Stardom is just an uneasy seat on top of a tricky toboggan. Being a star is merely perching at the head of the downgrade. A competent featured player can last a lifetime. A star, a year or two. There\'s all that agony of finding suitable stories, keeping in character, maintaining illusion."', '"Character,Illusion,Two"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402391', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefd', '"I liked the name Frederick Bickel and I wish now I had left it as it was. After all, Theodore Bikel, whose name was similar though spelled differently, didn\'t change his, and he did all right."', '"Change,Name,Wish"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402392', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefd', 'An actor has no more right to be temperamental than a bank clerk.', '"Bank,Right,More"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402393', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefd', '"It has been my experience that work on the screen clarifies stage portrayals and vice versa. You learn to make your face express more in making movies, and in working for the theater you have a sense of greater freedom."', '"Work,Freedom,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402394', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Naturally, business and pleasure can be readily combined, but a certain balance should exist, and the latter should not predominate over the former."', '"Business,Balance,Pleasure"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402395', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Today\'s date, the eighteenth of May, should sometime become an occasion of great international celebration, for on this day ten years ago the first Peace Conference opened at The Hague."', '"Peace,Great,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402396', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Indeed; peace literature is almost exclusively read, though to good effect, by pacifists, while what is needed is the canvassing of those who have not so far been won to the cause."', '"Peace,Good,Literature"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402397', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"But I feel convinced, and I venture even to prophesy in this regard, that the time will come when there will also be a minister of peace in the cabinet, seated beside the ministers of war."', '"War,Time,Peace"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402398', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"It has since been agreed that speeches given in English will be translated into French and vice versa, and even into German and Italian when necessary. No doubt translations into Esperanto will also soon be in demand."', '"Will,Doubt,Soon"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402399', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"To read the report of a discussion in which arguments for and against are presented, in which a subject has been covered from different points of view, with new ideas advanced - this is far more instructive than to read a brief account of the resolution passed on the matter."', '"View,New,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402400', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"By a great man, however, we mean a man who, because of his spiritual gifts, his character, and other qualities, deserves to be called great and who as a result earns the power to influence others."', '"Power,Great,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402401', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"A sign that a peace association is going adrift is its exclusion of other political parties, with whom it could collaborate effectively on most of the problems besetting the cause of peace."', '"Peace,Political,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402402', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"As a result of my study, I came to the conclusion that a common supreme authority was undesirable."', '"Result,Authority,Conclusion"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402403', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"I would have thought it possible to choose delegates for these larger conferences who, even if they could not speak the principal languages, could at least understand them or could have friends seated beside them who could keep them informed on essential points."', '"Speak,Principal,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402404', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', 'I would rather propose a bureau somewhat similar to that which we have in the Universal Postal Union.', '"Universal,Rather,Would"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402405', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Indeed, whenever a new idea is developed, as for example ballooning, warfare immediately takes possession."', '"New,Indeed,Example"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402406', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Nevertheless, this type of propaganda has a special value, for it serves to convince those who sign the appeal, of the necessity for carrying on propaganda; so a corps of propagandists, if I may use the term, is thus trained."', '"Value,Special,Propaganda"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402407', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"On the other hand, the waging of peace as a science, as an art, is in its infancy. But we can trace its growth, its steady progress, and the time will come when there will be particular individuals designated to assume responsibility for and leadership of this movement."', '"Leadership,Science,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402408', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Peace congresses often start by dealing with some of the less important questions in excessive detail, so at the end there is no time to discuss the most important problems."', '"Time,Peace,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402409', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"The aspect of congresses and such meetings generally to which I attach the greatest importance is the discussion. That is why people assemble: to hear different opinions, rather than to pass resolutions."', '"Meetings,People,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402410', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"The interparliamentary conference should, in my opinion, direct its particular attention to the preparation of the next Hague Conference, the diplomatic conference, the conference of governments."', '"Preparation,Opinion,Attention"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402411', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', 'The last Hague Conference has in the meantime expressed its opinion that a body should be established which could prepare for the work involved more effectively than has hitherto proved possible.', '"Work,Body,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402412', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"There are in most states one or two ministers of war, one of whom is the minister of naval affairs."', '"War,Two,Minister"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402413', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"There are many members of parliament present here who know as well as I do that, if a man has not already been converted, it will require a great deal more than a letter of appeal to achieve conversion."', '"Great,Man,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402414', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"There are those who believe we have need of more literature, of a large international publishing house, of a great peace newspaper, or the like. I am rather skeptical about this idea."', '"Peace,Great,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402415', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', 'There is one criticism which cannot be leveled at interparliamentary conferences but which is applicable to a great extent to peace congresses: the meetings waste time.', '"Time,Peace,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402416', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"This is the task, I think, of a letter movement. But it should be set up only in states where a significant response can be achieved, for a letter movement necessarily presupposes a strong organization."', '"Organization,Task,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402417', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"Waging war we understand, but not waging peace, or at any rate less consciously so."', '"War,Peace,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402418', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', 'Warfare has been marvelously developed. It will soon be impossible to raise it to further heights.', '"Impossible,Will,Heights"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402419', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"We have had such a letter movement on two occasions in Denmark when more than a quarter of the adult Danish population participated. Such an achievement, however, demands a really great effort and also a great deal of money."', '"Money,Great,Achievement"', '2023-05-29 12:10:00', '2023-05-29 12:10:00'),
	('402420', '6110d4a59c759c204c24fefe', '"We have long possessed the art of war and the science of war, which have been evolved in the minutest detail."', '"War,Science,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402421', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I swing between procrastination and being really thorough so either way things aren\'t getting done quickly.', '"Way,Done,Swing"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402422', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I know it\'s really square but I\'m one of those people who piles on the factor 50 as soon as I\'m outside.', '"People,Know,Outside"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402423', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I only unwind at facials and massages.', '"Unwind,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402424', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'Being short works for me.', '"Me,Short,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402425', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I always have to have breakfast before I leave the house, even if it\'s 4 A.M. and I\'m not hungry."', '"Breakfast,Always,Hungry"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402426', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I\'m not very glamorous.', '"Glamorous,Very"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402427', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I don\'t have an iPod! It\'s never appealed to me, really."', '"Me,Never,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402428', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I love hotels for their solitude and comfort, but I believe a seedy one can have as much promise as a plush one."', '"Love,Believe,Solitude"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402429', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I\'m one of these people that if I have a nice holiday - like I have had in Turkey repeatedly - I go back a lot.', '"People,Back,Holiday"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402430', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I\'m terrified of bugs and I travel with sprays, lotions, potions; the lot. I have to check the room before I go to sleep and if I come across a bug and fail to remove it I have to sleep in a separate room as I\'m paranoid that I\'ll be taken advantage of as I sleep."', '"Travel,Sleep,Room"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402431', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I used to be absolutely addicted to the gym and I do still love it.', '"Love,Gym,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402432', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I couldn\'t sustain myself if I skimped on food - I work 16-hour days, I need the energy, I can\'t afford to be stingy on what I eat."', '"Work,Food,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402433', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I went to a very academic school that actually - when I got to the point of wanting to pursue acting, they just had no idea how to do that, because all of their contacts were very academic."', '"School,Acting,Point"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402434', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I was very much into science when I was young - I wanted to be a marine biologist, then I wanted to be a doctor, and then something else, I was always changing."', '"Science,Doctor,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402435', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"I\'m fully aware that \'Doctor Who\' will always, always be part of my life, and that\'s not something I would run away from in the slightest. I wear it with pride, definitely."', '"Life,Doctor,Pride"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402436', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', '"The way sci-fi works, you can never die."', '"Die,Way,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402437', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I constantly make lists and itineraries and then can\'t stick to any of them.', '"Stick,Make,Lists"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402438', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I appreciate individualism.', '"Individualism,Appreciate"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402439', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'My own style is one of not much effort.', '"Effort,Style,My Own"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402440', '6110d4a59c759c204c24feff', 'I\'ve had journalists beg me to please say something negative about my estate.', '"Me,Negative,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402441', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'I began to understand the challenges that first-generation college students and students of color have in college.', '"Challenges,Understand,Color"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402442', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'I was fortunate to grow up in a middle-class home with two hardworking parents who enjoyed both reading and mathematics.', '"Home,Grow,Mathematics"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402443', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"Speak up. You have to project! If people can\'t hear you, it doesn\'t matter what you say."', '"People,Speak,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402444', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'It is part of the work of education to have substantive relationships with your students.', '"Education,Work,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402445', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"In life sciences, we find a reasonable balance between men and women. In engineering and computer science, we have a major problem. A very small percentage of women will be in computer science."', '"Life,Science,Women"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402446', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"My mother was an English teacher who decided to become a math teacher, and she used me as a guinea pig at home. My father had been a math teacher and then went to work at a steel mill because, frankly, he could make more money doing that."', '"Work,Money,Home"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402447', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"Computer games tend to be boys\' games, warlike games with more violence. We have not spent enough time thinking through how to encourage more girls to be involved in computing before coming to college so they can see a possible career in information technology."', '"Time,Technology,Thinking"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402448', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'I wanted to find ways for colleges and universities to become involved with public schools to help young people prepare for college.', '"People,Help,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402449', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"It is exciting to work with students thinking about issues of the day, from closing the achievement gap to finding a cure for cancer."', '"Work,Thinking,Achievement"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402450', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'There is something exciting about being in an environment in which it\'s really cool to be smart.', '"Cool,Smart,Environment"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402451', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"What people don\'t realize is that everybody needs support, one way or another."', '"Support,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402452', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'I guarantee the people who study are going to be successful. Nothing can replace hard work.', '"Work,Hard Work,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402453', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', '"When you give of yourself, it\'s draining."', '"Yourself,Draining,Give"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402454', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff00', 'Rich kids work hard. Most black kids aren\'t working hard enough.', '"Work,Black,Rich"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402455', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Technology is a gift of God. After the gift of life it is perhaps the greatest of God\'s gifts. It is the mother of civilizations, of arts and of sciences."', '"Life,God,Technology"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402456', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'A good scientist is a person with original ideas. A good engineer is a person who makes a design that works with as few original ideas as possible. There are no prima donnas in engineering.', '"Good,Design,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402457', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Aviation is the branch of engineering that is least forgiving of mistakes.', '"Mistakes,Engineering,Aviation"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402458', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The pain of childbirth is not remembered. It\'s the child that\'s remembered.', '"Pain,Child,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402459', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Every orchid or rose or lizard or snake is the work of a dedicated and skilled breeder. There are thousands of people, amateurs and professionals, who devote their lives to this business. Now imagine what will happen when the tools of genetic engineering become accessible to these people."', '"Work,Business,Snake"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402460', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'There is a great satisfaction in building good tools for other people to use.', '"Good,Great,Satisfaction"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402461', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The public knows that human beings are fallible. Only people blinded by ideology fall into the trap of believing in their own infallibility.', '"People,Own,Fall"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402462', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"The PhD system is the real root of the evil of academic snobbery. People who have PhDs consider themselves a priesthood, and inventors generally don\'t have PhDs."', '"People,Real,Evil"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402463', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Unfortunately the global warming hysteria, as I see it, is driven by politics more than by science."', '"Politics,Science,Global Warming"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402464', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Biology is now bigger than physics, as measured by the size of budgets, by the size of the workforce, or by the output of major discoveries; and biology is likely to remain the biggest part of science through the twenty-first century."', '"Science,Biology,Physics"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402465', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"The technologies that raise the fewest ethical problems are those that work on a human scale, brightening the lives of individual people."', '"Work,Problems,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402466', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The climate-studies people who work with models always tend to overestimate their models. They come to believe models are real and forget they are only models.', '"Work,Believe,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402467', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"I see a bright future for the biotechnology industry when it follows the path of the computer industry, the path that von Neumann failed to foresee, becoming small and domesticated rather than big and centralized."', '"Future,Path,See"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402468', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"We have no reason to think that climate change is harmful if you look at the world as a whole. Most places, in fact, are better off being warmer than being colder. And historically, the really bad times for the environment and for people have been the cold periods rather than the warm periods."', '"Change,Environmental,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402469', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The question that will decide our destiny is not whether we shall expand into space. It is: shall we be one species or a million? A million species will not exhaust the ecological niches that are awaiting the arrival of intelligence.', '"Space,Intelligence,Destiny"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402470', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The technologies which have had the most profound effects on human life are usually simple.', '"Life,Simple,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402471', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'I have the freedom to do what I want... bright people to talk to every day.', '"Freedom,Day,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402472', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"I don\'t believe in technological determinism, especially not in biology and medicine. We have strong laws to keep doctors from monkeying around with humans that will remain in place. It\'s simply not true that everything that is technologically possible gets done."', '"Believe,True,Biology"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402473', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Unfortunately, things are different in climate science because the arguments have become heavily politicised. To say that the dogmas are wrong has become politically incorrect."', '"Science,Climate,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402474', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Successful technologies often begin as hobbies. Jacques Cousteau invented scuba diving because he enjoyed exploring caves. The Wright brothers invented flying as a relief from the monotony of their normal business of selling and repairing bicycles.', '"Business,Normal,Flying"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402475', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The purpose of thinking about the future is not to predict it but to raise people\'s hopes.', '"Future,Thinking,Purpose"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402476', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'It has become part of the accepted wisdom to say that the twentieth century was the century of physics and the twenty-first century will be the century of biology.', '"Wisdom,Biology,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402477', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'It\'s better to get mugged than to live a life of fear.', '"Life,Fear,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402478', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'It is characteristic of all deep human problems that they are not to be approached without some humor and some bewilderment.', '"Humor,Problems,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402479', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'You ask: what is the meaning or purpose of life? I can only answer with another question: do you think we are wise enough to read God\'s mind?', '"Life,God,Wise"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402480', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"What the world needs is a small, compact, flexible fusion technology that could make electricity where and when it is needed. The existing fusion program is leading to a huge source of centralized power, at a price that nobody except a government can afford."', '"Power,Technology,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402481', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'I don\'t think of myself predicting things. I\'m expressing possibilities. Things that could happen. To a large extent it\'s a question of how badly people want them to.', '"Myself,People,Possibilities"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402482', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The biologists have essentially been pushed aside. Al Gore\'s just an opportunist. The person who is really responsible for this overestimate of global warming is Jim Hansen. He consistently exaggerates all the dangers.', '"Global Warming,Person,Global"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402483', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"It\'s not going to be just humans colonizing space, it\'s going to be life moving out from the Earth, moving it into its kingdom. And the kingdom of life, of course, is going to be the universe."', '"Life,Space,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402484', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'I am saying that all predictions concerning climate are highly uncertain.', '"I Am,Climate,Saying"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402485', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Scepticism is as important for a good journalist as it is for a good scientist.', '"Good,Important,Scientist"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402486', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"The world of science and the world of literature have much in common. Each is an international club, helping to tie mankind together across barriers of nationality, race and language. I have been doubly lucky, being accepted as a member of both."', '"Science,Together,World"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402487', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Younger people have so many opportunities. I don\'t see any pessimism among them.', '"People,See,Younger"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402488', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"It\'s as great a part of the human adventure to invent things as to understand them. John Randall wasn\'t a great scientist, but he was a great inventor. There\'s been lots more like him, and it\'s a shame they don\'t get Nobel Prizes."', '"Great,Shame,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402489', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The idea that global warming is the most important problem facing the world is total nonsense and is doing a lot of harm.', '"World,Important,Global Warming"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402490', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The fact that the climate is getting warmer doesn\'t scare me at all. There\'s no reason why one should be scared.', '"Me,Climate,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402491', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Just because you see pictures of glaciers falling into the ocean doesn\'t mean anything bad is happening. This is something that happens all the time. It\'s part of the natural cycle of things. We know from measurements that glaciers have been melting for 200 years at least.', '"Time,Bad,See"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402492', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'Lucky individuals in each generation find technology appropriate to their needs.', '"Technology,Generation,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402493', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"Many of the technologies that are now racing ahead most rapidly, replacing human workers in factories and offices with machines, making stockholders richer and workers poorer, are indeed tending to accentuate the existing inequalities in the distribution of wealth."', '"Wealth,Ahead,Indeed"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402494', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"The marketplace judges technologies by their practical effectiveness, by whether they succeed or fail to do the job they are designed to do."', '"Job,Succeed,Judges"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402495', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'The important thing is that we now have the tools to sequence all kinds of animals and plants and microbes - as well as humans. It is not important that we didn\'t actually finish the human sequence yet.', '"Important,Plants,Finish"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402496', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', 'I like people who are working on practical things and who are working in teams. It\'s not so important to get the glory. It\'s much more important to get something that works. It\'s a better way to live.', '"Better,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402497', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"If you start out with a tragic view of life, then anything since is just a bonus."', '"Life,View,Start"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402498', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff01', '"I\'m a mathematician, basically. What I do is look around for problems where I can find useful applications for mathematics. All I do, really, is the math, and other people have the ideas."', '"Look,Mathematics,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402499', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff02', '"Good design begins with honesty, asks tough questions, comes from collaboration and from trusting your intuition."', '"Good,Design,Honesty"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402500', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff02', '"We were promised a simpler life, and technology has only complicated our lives."', '"Life,Technology,Complicated"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402501', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff02', 'We think there\'s a huge opportunity in smaller vehicles. Smaller vehicles done in an American way.', '"Opportunity,Way,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402502', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"My hope is that light, flexible architecture might bring about a new and open society."', '"Hope,Society,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402503', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"We have big, big problems - flooding, earthquake, and many foolish things which now people are doing - I mean, these self-made catastrophes. We are able to give to every man on the street the possibilities to help himself. And to fight for this was one of my duties."', '"Fight,Man,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402504', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', 'My architecture is the architecture of survival.', '"Architecture,Survival"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402505', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"Everything man is doing in architecture is to try to go against nature. Of course we have to understand nature to know how far we have to go against nature. The secret, I think, of the future is not doing too much. All architects have the tendency to do too much."', '"Nature,Future,Architecture"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402506', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"I have never been satisfied with a piece of work I have been actively involved in, and would never want to be."', '"Work,Never,Satisfied"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402507', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"My architectural drive was to design new types of buildings to help poor people, especially following natural disasters and catastrophes... I will use whatever time is left to me to keep doing what I have been doing, which is to help humanity."', '"Time,Design,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402508', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"I have only one dream. It is the oldest of humanity, of man, in time. It is paradise. I would like to give paradise to everyone."', '"Time,Man,Humanity"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402509', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', 'Buildings are \'humane\' only when they promote peaceful human co-existence.', '"Buildings,Human,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402510', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"Most architects think in drawings, or did think in drawings; today, they think on the computer monitor. I always tried to think three dimensionally. The interior eye of the brain should be not flat but three dimensional so that everything is an object in space. We are not living in a two-dimensional world."', '"Space,Today,Brain"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402511', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff03', '"Why should we build very large spaces when they are not necessary? We can design halls spanning several kilometres and covering a whole city, but we have to ask, what does it really make? What does society really need?"', '"Society,Design,City"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402512', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I\'ll never forget where I\'m from. It\'s essential to remain humble and evolving.', '"Humble,Never Forget,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402513', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"When a doctor is performing an operation, his mind cannot be somewhere else. And it\'s the same with actors. You have to commit yourself mind, body and soul to a project in order to do justice to it."', '"Doctor,Justice,Soul"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402514', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I\'m a human being before anything else.', '"Anything,Human,Human Being"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402515', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I did not particularly enjoy modeling. I felt I was only utilizing 10 or 20 percent of my abilities. In India, it\'s just another job."', '"Job,Enjoy,Modeling"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402516', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I think even the most beautiful person looks stupid on Skype.', '"Most Beautiful,Beautiful,Stupid"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402517', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I\'ve never told anyone this before, but I\'m an obsessive-compulsive. I go back to my hotel room every evening and put the coat hangers back in order and open my bag and rearrange it. It takes a lot of my time, but if I don\'t do it I can\'t sleep."', '"Time,Evening,Hotel"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402518', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I definitely need to date someone who is calm.', '"Calm,Someone,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402519', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"All people - African, European, American - worry about being different. But I\'ve learned that the traits we\'d rush to get rid of are the very ones that others desire. People always covet what they don\'t have. That\'s why we should look at ourselves every now and then and say, \'I\'m proud of myself. I like the way I\'m made.\'"', '"Myself,Look,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402520', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I love going into a country and just blending.', '"Love,Country,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402521', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I wouldn\'t want to do a Bollywood film per se, but I would like to do an Indian-language film. For some reason I think Bollywood has become synonymous with commercial cinema, which is song and dance and everything that is larger than life, and I am interested in the reality."', '"Life,Reality,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402522', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I\'ve learned to develop a thick skin, but you\'re bound to be affected when you read something bad about yourself in the paper and it\'s rubbed in your face over and over."', '"Face,Yourself,Skin"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402523', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"Having grown up in Bombay, from the day you\'re born, you have absolute freedom to choose who you want to be."', '"Freedom,Day,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402524', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'If a cream can give you confidence then you really have to check your whole confidence department in the first place.', '"Confidence,Place,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402525', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I like working on big budget films.', '"Big,Budget,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402526', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"Here\'s another secret - I have really big feet. I\'m a size ten, so every opportunity I get I buy myself shoes."', '"Myself,Opportunity,Shoes"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402527', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I feel like the history between Israel and Palestine has a lot in common with the history between India and Pakistan.', '"History,Feel,Palestine"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402528', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I keep saying I\'m not at all famous in my own country, because people do not think I have done anything for India."', '"Famous,People,Country"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402529', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I always imagined that I would learn something each time that I would take to a new project, then I realized that each new project poses a completely different challenge."', '"Time,New,Challenge"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402530', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I guess confidence is the only thing that I take from project to project, but I\'m always open to learning everybody\'s style - the director, the actor I\'m working with."', '"Learning,Confidence,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402531', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I tell you why I like Chanel so much: when I started off, no one wanted to give me clothes to wear. Absolutely no one! All the labels said, \'Who is she?\' But Chanel believed in me from the very beginning."', '"Me,Beginning,Clothes"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402532', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I\'m glad I\'m a strong person.', '"Person,Strong,Glad"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402533', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"As the world\'s getting filled with temptations, we\'re getting a bit frivolous and a bit fickle."', '"World,Fickle,Frivolous"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402534', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"Anybody, anywhere in the world, all they want is to be free, to choose what they want to do without having someone tell them how to do it."', '"World,Free,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402535', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'There\'s one disturbing notion throughout India that light skin is more attractive than dark.', '"Light,Skin,Dark"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402536', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"When you doubt one thing about yourself, you start thinking there\'s also something wrong with your hair, your body, your clothes, your accent."', '"Thinking,Yourself,Hair"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402537', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'In L.A. you hear all these stories of people being filmed in their own homes through their windows. I think that is so scary.', '"People,Own,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402538', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I think it\'s important to be extremely proud of one\'s origins, especially when you are a foreign actress with ethnic features."', '"Important,Proud,Ethnic"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402539', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I am first and foremost an actress of Indian origin.', '"I Am,Indian,First"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402540', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I actually didn\'t mind school, and I enjoyed university and college."', '"Mind,School,University"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402541', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"A lot of the younger Indian generation are either IT geniuses or doctors - the number of doctors I\'ve seen in L.A. who are Indian is just crazy. So it is a very common thing. Or an accountant! That again is a very, very big thing."', '"Crazy,Generation,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402542', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I feel like this whole idea of wanting something that you don\'t really have is also very American in a way.', '"Way,Feel,American"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402543', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'Everything big-budget or stereotypical I was offered after \'Slumdog Millionaire\' was a huge no-no.', '"Everything,Millionaire,After"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402544', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I don\'t think Bollywood is only mindless cinema, but a lot of films they churn out are not films that I completely enjoy watching."', '"Cinema,Watching,Enjoy"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402545', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I absolutely love London; it is one of my favourite cities in the world.', '"Love,World,London"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402546', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I find it very interesting these days that films are bringing in so many people of different ethnicities, and I\'m proud to be a part of that cultural shift."', '"People,Proud,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402547', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"Of course I\'m going to marry, but I don\'t know when."', '"Know,Going,Course"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402548', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I feel being an actress is probably not half as difficult as being a mother, and I do not know when I will be ready for that kind of a decision."', '"Decision,Difficult,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402549', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"In terms of romantic films, all-time romantic films, I really like \'Gone With the Wind.\' And I realize I sound so cliched saying that, but there\'s something so absolutely romantic about it."', '"Romantic,Wind,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402550', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"One of my favorite actors is Javier Bardem, he always challenges his previous roles, and basically does the unexpected."', '"Challenges,Unexpected,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402551', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"I went to an all-girls\' Christian convent school run by nuns. It was fun, but when I was 15, I said, \'Mum, that\'s it - I need to go where there are some boys.\'"', '"Fun,School,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402552', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', '"Indian celebrities have the media and fans permanently outside their homes, and that would make me really uncomfortable."', '"Me,Media,Fans"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402553', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff04', 'I\'d like to jump out of a plane. I have a fear of heights I\'d like to face.', '"Fear,Face,Jump"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402554', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'You can pull off anything if you have the right attitude. Being cool is whatever you think it is. Own your style.', '"Attitude,Cool,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402555', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I would like to sit down with Emily Dickinson, Virginia Woolf, PJ Harvey, and Bjork. That would be a good dinner in my mind. Strong women. I think I would enjoy that."', '"Women,Good,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402556', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I love to have massages, I think it\'s really important to relax. In New York, I usually go to Massage Williamsburg or Great Jones Spa."', '"Love,Great,Relax"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402557', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"Being a tomboy worked to my advantage in fashion. I\'m known as the androgynous girl - I\'ve used it in a way that works for me. I\'ve never felt a pressure to change myself. I do own a few Rick Owens dresses - they\'re more like long tank tops, though."', '"Change,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402558', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"My routine is really simple. I wash my face with Bioderma Sensibio H2O, and I exfoliate around once a week. I then use an oil-free moisturiser, and that\'s pretty much it."', '"Simple,Face,Routine"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402559', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"Never be scared to cut your own hair, but take it easy and never go too far."', '"Hair,Never,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402560', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I never really wear any make-up on my face, like foundation or anything - and I really wouldn\'t advise that you leave that on your skin at night - but I do often leave on my eye make-up overnight. I actually prefer it the next day; it looks more worn-in."', '"Night,Face,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402561', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I get out of bed, brush my teeth, wash my face, put on moisturiser, put on clothes, and leave. Four minutes. I like to shower at night so I can roll out of bed."', '"Night,Face,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402562', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I guess I like more of the skinny jeans. I\'m not very fond of all the stretch, so I try to avoid too much stretch fabric."', '"Jeans,Skinny,Avoid"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402563', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I was a little biker girl. I thought it was cool; everyone else thought it was really weird. The other little girls were all in these pretty dresses, and my mum bought me this black, studded leather jacket, which I loved."', '"Cool,Black,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402564', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I\'ve been travelling around the U.K., actually getting to see places. I\'m so lucky that I am able to travel with work, but you don\'t often get to experience them properly."', '"Work,Experience,Travel"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402565', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'I want to carry on modelling for years to come.', '"Want,Carry,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402566', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I\'ve been so blessed to have the career I have had, so each and every shoot and job is a privilege for me to be at."', '"Me,Blessed,Shoot"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402567', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"It\'s important to think about the bigger picture, especially if we are given these platforms. We can make a difference."', '"Picture,Make A Difference,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402568', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'I grew up playing soccer with the boys - quite far from reading magazines.', '"Far,Reading,Up"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402569', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I love the process - collaborating with the photographers, traveling, and seeing different cultures. My mother always said I would regret it if I didn\'t do it. And I think she was right."', '"Love,Regret,Process"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402570', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'Denim should always be comfortable; jeans should protect you. They are workwear.', '"Always,Comfortable,Jeans"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402571', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'There\'s a special feeling that you get from Chanel that you don\'t get from any other show.', '"Special,Feeling,Show"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402572', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"It\'s hard when people ask me to walk in a different way than I would naturally. I don\'t think my walk is particularly elegant if you compare it to other girls, but it fits my personality."', '"Personality,Walk,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402573', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'I\'m always in an Alexander Wang t-shirt or tank top and Acne jeans. I can just throw that on and be myself.', '"Myself,T-Shirt,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402574', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'I don\'t really wear lipstick.', '"Lipstick,Wear,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402575', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I am quite \'natural\' in the sense that I do not worry too much about the way I look, and I like a casual look. I do not wear make-up if I do not need to."', '"Look,I Am,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402576', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"To have power naps! In the past months, I have learned to have them everywhere I go, and that is key for my health. To eat healthy food is also essential - especially fruit, for the vitamins."', '"Health,Power,Food"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402577', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', '"I do a bit of yoga - by myself, not classes. I like to go for long walks and to garden."', '"Myself,Long,Garden"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402578', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff05', 'Beauty doesn\'t have to be the perfect image. It\'s more interesting to have something a bit off.', '"Beauty,Perfect,Image"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402579', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Every man needs a good, solid watch. My favorite watch is the Presidential Rolex. I own many watches, but this one is usually the one on my wrist. I buy mine in the Diamond District in New York City. Classic."', '"Good,Man,City"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402580', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"In school, my favorite subject was math. That\'s where I learned to count money."', '"Money,School,Where"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402581', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I felt like for what I needed, Bad Boy got me... they got me covered. Especially Puff, man. He\'s going to be the first billionaire rap entertainer. At the end of the day, they need me. Other artists-labels don\'t need me, but Bad Boy and Puff needs me. And I need them. It goes both ways."', '"Man,End Of The Day,Bad Boy"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402582', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'Money is the most important thing because there might be a time when you have no label behind you and you have to carry yourself. Money is the only thing that can shield you.', '"Money,Time,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402583', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I was never officially signed with Akon, but it was a shopping deal. That was around the time he was going through some problems with his label at Interscope. I waited, but when a deal didn\'t happen, I just went out on my own."', '"Time,Problems,Shopping"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402584', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I\'ve tried every kind of bottled water, but Poland Spring is my go-to. I always have room-temperature bottles of it on side of stage for post-performance."', '"Water,Always,Stage"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402585', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'I was born in Morocco and lived there until I was 13; I\'m really proud of my heritage.', '"Heritage,Proud,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402586', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"At the end of the day, you got to learn from people that been through what you been through; they help you learn from your mistakes."', '"End Of The Day,Day,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402587', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"It\'s Fendi. French, Fendi, both start with an F... I fell in love with it. Smells like grown-man cologne."', '"Love,Start,Cologne"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402588', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'You can\'t expect to make all this money and not go through problems. You can\'t expect God to give you everything you want without taking something away.', '"God,Money,Problems"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402589', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Besides my son, music is the most important thing to me. I always have music on in my car and playing at house, and I\'m in the studio or performing every night. I like Beats by Dre for headphones, and Bang & Olufsen soundsystems."', '"Car,Music,Night"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402590', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"My dream pet? I like a couple of them, man: monkey, I love dogs. See, tigers, I don\'t know - I can\'t be playing with something like that. A monkey, I can handle it. A dog, yeah; I would get a monkey."', '"Love,Pet,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402591', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"When I had a kid and I went through my drama and situation, I respected my father more because it kinda made me understand what he went through with me."', '"Me,Father,Drama"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402592', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'I like colorful stuff. I like wearing stuff that nobody is wearing. That\'s why I wear the bear hat. I\'ll wear the whole mink.', '"Hat,Nobody,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402593', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Is it important to have a crew behind me? No, it\'s important to have me behind them. That\'s how I look at it. You can\'t just roll with a situation like you\'re depending on somebody to help you. You\'re supposed to help the situation, whatever the situation is that you\'re in."', '"Look,Me,Situation"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402594', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I speak from the heart. Certain people follow lyricists and people that put words on a dictionary together, and this and that. I\'m more of a rapper that speaks how I feel. I just tell it how it is."', '"Heart,Together,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402595', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Every time I look at Twitter, there\'s always somebody showing support."', '"Time,Look,Support"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402596', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I used to play soccer when I was in Morocco, but I was more of a basketball player. I played high school basketball, I played AAU basketball."', '"School,More,High School"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402597', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I feel like, you know, some people like to wear colorful stuff. Some people like to be blacked down, and some people just want to be colorful. Some people just have weird problems. I\'m never going to wear a pink sweater. Some people just do it because they feel like they can do it."', '"Problems,Feel,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402598', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'The hardest situation to pick up a girl in is ... in church and in Morocco on Ramadan. On Ramadan or one of those religious days? Try to pick up a girl is bananas.', '"Situation,Church,Girl"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402599', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I have been a fan of Versace for so long, watching people like Biggie, Puff, Jay-Z."', '"Long,People,Watching"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402600', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'Whatever rappers wear is cool to people.', '"Cool,People,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402601', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Umm... I don\'t judge my relationship with Puff or Bad Boy according to other people or past artists. At the end of the day, you are in charge of your career, and you can\'t depend on no man to do anything for you. I\'ve learned to judge relationships with a person on myself and that person, not what they have done with previous people."', '"Relationship,Myself,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402602', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Coming from Morocco was just different, man. It\'s a third-world country, and you are trying to make it happen. That\'s all it is. I didn\'t have any problem hooking up with the black kids because I\'m from North Africa. And as far as Latinos, we are all the same."', '"Black,Man,Make It Happen"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402603', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'I\'m not going to go to a producer that\'s going to take me in a studio and charge me my whole budget and give me a fake head nod. I\'m just trying to make good music. I appreciate everybody that\'s supporting me.', '"Good,Music,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402604', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Before I had a son, I used to look at my father\'s example: he left me, he left my mother. When I had a son, I got caught in the same situation that his mother don\'t want me to see him. I started looking at my father in a different light."', '"Look,Me,Light"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402605', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', 'I don\'t want to sound like Ross; I don\'t want to sound like Puff. I want to make my own music: French Montana.', '"Music,My Own,Sound"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402606', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Besides buying a mansion or something, everything I wanted I always got. I\'m just ready to invest it and save it. Otherwise, life can hit you, but you can\'t go back to working at Home Depot. That\'s why I always just be stacking."', '"Life,Home,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402607', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"Sometimes I take off my skully and wear glasses, so I\'ve gotta brush and make sure my hairline is straight."', '"Glasses,Sometimes,Wear"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402608', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff06', '"I came from battling, knowing about the lyrics. All that\'s cool, but if you want people to love you, you have to talk to them about what they go through."', '"Love,Cool,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402609', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff07', 'Buster Keaton is my hero.', '"Hero,Buster,Keaton"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402610', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff07', 'Everyone seems to have this awareness of Charlie Chaplin because he was a really good businessman while Buster Keaton wasn\'t.', '"Good,Awareness,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402611', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff07', '"I come from a heavy-lidded people. My family, you\'ll see pictures of them, and it\'s the same thing all the way back to Scotland."', '"Family,Way,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402612', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"It is nice to be the most expensive Dutchman, and it is nice for my agent and for Ajax. But it does not matter to me whether I cost ??m or ??50m or ??00m. I just need to make sure that I do my own thing."', '"Me,Matter,My Own"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402613', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"My quality is my intuition. I can\'t just ignore that, can I? Then I\'d be a player of whom there are a thousand of my age."', '"Age,Quality,Ignore"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402614', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"Normally, midfielders only pass the ball, but I dribble as well."', '"Ball,Well,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402615', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"I like to watch the great players, the ones who are technically good and understand the game. I try to see how they move."', '"Good,Great,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402616', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"When I was in Barcelona, people thought I would join them, but that\'s not the case. Everyone knows that I think Barcelona is a beautiful club, but I don\'t know if I should see my career as a city trip."', '"Beautiful,City,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402617', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"I try not to pay attention to talk of comparisons. I only want to focus on myself. It is good to hear that people are talking like that, but the truth is I am not at Cruyff\'s level of talent, and I never will be, so it is not something I think about."', '"Truth,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402618', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'Barcelona have always been a dream club for me.', '"Me,Always,Club"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402619', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"For me, honestly, I would like to play with Messi one day."', '"Me,Day,One Day"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402620', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"Often I\'d say I understood the coach, then do my own thing on the field."', '"My Own,Own,Field"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402621', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"I love this style: get the ball back quickly, then play possession with so many combinations. When you watch that, you get the feeling you want to go out on the pitch and play football with your friends and just enjoy yourself. City and Barcelona are great examples."', '"Love,Great,Football"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402622', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"I have always been a midfielder, and I remain a midfielder."', '"Always,Been,Remain"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402623', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"Most good players play on intuition. Everyone has a little, but I don\'t know if you can learn it."', '"Good,Know,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402624', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"When I am on the pitch, I play on intuition, but I think a lot about the game as well."', '"Game,I Am,Intuition"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402625', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'I try to have a picture when I receive the ball and know where everyone is. That\'s one of the most important things for a midfielder.', '"Picture,Important,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402626', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'I\'d love to play with Ajax against Barcelona.', '"Love,Play,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402627', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"I already watched Barcelona as a kid, and then, when I was a bit more aware of the game, you had the Guardiola era with all their successes. That turned me into an even bigger fan."', '"Me,Game,More"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402628', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'It\'s not like I am going to Barcelona as a tourist who is there to watch Messi in action. I am not going to say that I will bench Busquets or anything! But I think I have a good chance of getting plenty of minutes.', '"Good,Chance,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402629', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', '"If you end up at a superior club, you will play with world-class players all over the pitch."', '"Will,End,Club"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402630', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'I think I was the last teenager to get WhatsApp.', '"Last,Think,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402631', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff08', 'PSG would have been an excellent choice. They did everything to get me.', '"Me,Choice,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402632', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"When I first started, I\'d play to a few people. My mum would invite everyone she knew and the venue was filled."', '"People,Everyone,She"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402633', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"At the age of 11 I did my first open mic show, and it was one of those lightning-bolt moments where I suddenly found what I wanted to do."', '"Age,Open,Mic"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402634', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I followed my gut and my subconscious told me the kind of music I wanted to create. But it wasn\'t easy.', '"Music,Me,Create"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402635', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I remember in 2016 when I got signed to my record label Good Soldier, which is a very small indie label. They took a big risk on me because ballads were the furthest thing from cool at the time."', '"Cool,Time,Good"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402636', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I was quite a different child, I felt isolated. In time, that level of being with yourself crystallises who you are, and you can see what other people are without being blinded by what they want from you."', '"Time,Yourself,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402637', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"That\'s the best thing about being with an indie label, it feels like a family. If it\'s a major label, they put so much pressure on every single."', '"Best,Family,Pressure"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402638', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'Songwriting really anchored me.', '"Me,Songwriting,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402639', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Every time I do something new, it makes me a bit stronger. Playing huge shows, being invited to play with Nile Rodgers after the Brits - all are mindblowing and I have a great team around me who are empowering. It makes all the difference."', '"Time,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402640', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I\'ve been writing since I was 11. But I don\'t write with a pen, I just sing at the piano with one eye shut like a pirate."', '"Pen,Eye,Writing"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402641', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I heard that your subconscious is on the right side. I always shut my right eye when I play, or both eyes. I feel like you go to a deeper place in your subconscious, and you tell the stories that are more deeply within you."', '"Eyes,Feel,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402642', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Growing up, I promised myself that if I was every lucky enough to have a hit and also a hit that I had written myself, I would never get tired of performing it. I would always be grateful for that."', '"Myself,Tired,Grateful"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402643', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'There was an open mic night when I was about 11 years old and I went and I played the songs that I\'d written in my bedroom and it was the first night where I felt like I was myself at school.', '"Myself,Night,Bedroom"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402644', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I find an apple before singing really, really helps... It\'s like there\'s something in the pectin in the apple that helps get rid of vocal clicks."', '"Singing,Find,Apple"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402645', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"When I first started writing songs, I was almost quite embarrassed that I couldn\'t read music and I still to this day don\'t really know what chords I\'m playing, I don\'t know the name of them."', '"Music,Day,Name"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402646', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Going to school, sort of not realising that caring about things was going to make me stand out and make me weird, and I think also being a redhead and being tall, bigger than the other kids... Anything that makes you different at school makes you a target."', '"Me,Caring,Weird"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402647', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'You know the way you tell your life story to a friend? I just told mine to a piano.', '"Life,Way,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402648', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"So when you\'re sat there and you\'re looking at a platinum disc on your wall, for a song you wrote on your own, it\'s like this is getting crazy, man. It\'s all crazy."', '"Man,Crazy,Song"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402649', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I was brought up in a bohemian household where my dad plays guitar and my mom plays piano just because they love it.', '"Love,Mom,Dad"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402650', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'All of my music teachers gave up on me one by one because I couldn\'t read music.', '"Music,Me,Teachers"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402651', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I\'m obsessed with American talk shows.', '"American,Talk,Obsessed"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402652', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Me and my mom were just watching the charts like, \'Why isn\'t it stopping?\' And now I\'ve got a platinum disc in my bedroom."', '"Mom,Me,Bedroom"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402653', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"At school I was really heavily dyslexic, so I really struggled academically with reading and writing."', '"School,Writing,Reading"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402654', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"All my songs are based on personal experience, and \'Lost Without You\' came out fully born."', '"Experience,Lost,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402655', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I was in a choir at school and we were part of the BBC Proms back in around 2002.', '"School,Back,Around"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402656', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I remember, a couple of years ago I was playing my first headline show, and it was to 100 people in St Pancras Old Church in London; and me and my mum were like, \'We don\'t know 100 people, how are we going to sell these tickets?\'"', '"Me,Remember,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402657', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I love the acoustic sets. Growing up, me and my dad would always watch those because we loved seeing the songs stripped back."', '"Love,Dad,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402658', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I\'m obsessed with Beyonce. She\'s just effervescent, I love her."', '"Love,She,Her"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402659', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I\'m on a group chat with my dad which he named \'Dearest Daughter\'. It\'s so sweet because I don\'t think he really understands that a group chat normally has more than two people but I love chatting with him in it anyway.', '"Love,Dad,Sweet"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402660', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'Selfies are one of those things I generally take but never post. It\'s more to remember the moment or what I\'m doing.', '"Moment,Remember,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402661', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'Being signed to a major label was never an option because I knew having the time to find out who you are without pressure from other people is so important.', '"Time,Pressure,People"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402662', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"The thing with \'Lost Without You\' is that for a long time I didn\'t feel like I could share it with people. When it came to releasing it, it was a cliff-diving moment."', '"Time,Moment,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402663', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I realised, however, that you can\'t sing when you\'re playing the violin - or at least I can\'t - and as that aspect of performing is important to me I shifted to the piano."', '"Me,Important,Violin"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402664', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Sometimes, when we\'re on tour, I\'ll find an empty room or a corner and I\'ll just sing. It heals something in me, be it some kind of isolation or loneliness. It\'s really quite beautiful that singing can do that."', '"Beautiful,Loneliness,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402665', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I wasn\'t cool at all when I was younger; no one wanted anything from me.', '"Cool,Me,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402666', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"Inspiring girls to write their stories and play their own instruments is something I\'m passionate about, as it\'s not championed."', '"Own,Play,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402667', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I do get star-struck, especially if they\'re icons like Florence Welch. I met her briefly at a studio and I did not act cool."', '"Cool,Act,Studio"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402668', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"There\'s no expectations at all. Every single person that turns up to a show, you really appreciate them. Every single radio interview you do - everything."', '"Expectations,Person,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402669', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', 'I really want to do a cover of Joan Armatrading.', '"Want,Cover,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402670', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I think, definitely, I was hugely influenced by - obviously like Adele and Florence the Machine. They were my complete idols growing up. But also, there were a lot of influences from my dad, like singer-songwriters of the \'70s like Carole King and James Taylor."', '"Dad,King,Idols"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402671', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff09', '"I never went out to make the music that people would like. I mean, I tried, because every teenager tries to do that. But in my heart, I\'d always come from gigs where I played upbeat guitar covers and I\'d start writing sad songs on the piano."', '"Sad,Music,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402672', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'There can be no happiness if the things we believe in are different from the things we do.', '"Happiness,Believe,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402673', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'To awaken quite alone in a strange town is one of the pleasantest sensations in the world.', '"Alone,World,Strange"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402674', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', '"Christmas... is not an external event at all, but a piece of one\'s home that one carries in one\'s heart."', '"Home,Christmas,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402675', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'Curiosity is the one thing invincible in Nature.', '"Nature,Curiosity,Invincible"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402676', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'The great and almost only comfort about being a woman is that one can always pretend to be more stupid than one is and no one is surprised.', '"Great,Stupid,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402677', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'Few are the giants of the soul who actually feel that the human race is their family circle.', '"Family,Soul,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402678', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', '"Absence is one of the most useful ingredients of family life, and to dose it rightly is an art like any other."', '"Life,Family,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402679', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', 'Pain and fear and hunger are effects of causes which can be foreseen and known: but sorrow is a debt which someone else makes for us.', '"Fear,Pain,Sorrow"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402680', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0a', '"If we are strong, and have faith in life and its richness of surprises, and hold the rudder steadily in our hands. I am sure we will sail into quiet and pleasent waters for our old age."', '"Life,Faith,Age"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402681', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', 'Whatever I ended up picking or choosing was always going to be a creative outlet for me.', '"Me,Always,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402682', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', 'Plan B is a plan to fail. You should always give 110% to what you plan to do for plan A.', '"Always,Plan,Fail"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402683', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', '"I really wanted to be a spy. I guess it\'s a bit like acting, where you play a role."', '"Acting,Guess,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402684', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', '"I knew my priority was acting, and school came second. If I had an audition and meetings, I did the school work later."', '"Work,Meetings,School"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402685', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', 'One of the great things about working for Netflix is that they haven\'t placed any restrictions on content or artistically.', '"Great,Great Things,Netflix"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402686', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', '"Acting was just something that came really naturally to me, and it was just something that I knew how to do."', '"Me,Acting,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402687', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', 'It\'s important for any child really to have somebody to back you up and let you follow your dream.', '"Important,Back,Follow"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402688', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', 'It\'s about not having doubt in your mind and staying focused and not having any preconceived notion about failure. It\'s just looking forward and staying positive.', '"Positive,Failure,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402689', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0b', '"I\'d been going to school up to the third term of year 11 at MLC, and there was no point in dropping out. Having gone through Year 12, there\'s so much that helps you acquire the knowledge you need. It helps you in life."', '"Life,Knowledge,School"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402690', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"Venice never quite seems real, but rather an ornate film set suspended on the water."', '"Water,Real,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402691', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', 'I don\'t want to be too \'classic\' because it\'s not in the DNA of Gucci. You need to be a little bit provocative.', '"DNA,Classic,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402692', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"All the drawings and sketches and clothes of Yves Saint Laurent in the \'70s were so colorful, so bright."', '"Clothes,Bright,Colorful"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402693', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"The idea of \'ferie,\' or summer break, is a long tradition of which all Italians, including myself, participate. It\'s a time to relax, reflect and recharge."', '"Time,Myself,Relax"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402694', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"When I joined Gucci in 2002, I immediately wanted to make a research trip into the archives because I\'d heard about how incredible they were, but I never had the opportunity to visit them."', '"Opportunity,Research,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402695', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I grew up in Rome, in actually what I would say was a liberal, open-minded family. My father was an architect and my mother was a teacher of art history, so it was sort of intellectual, and maybe a bit much for me when I was a child."', '"Family,History,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402696', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I think the \'70s are always inspiring to me. I was born then, so I have a lot of memories about how my parents were and what kinds of movies I was watching."', '"Movies,Memories,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402697', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', 'My biggest satisfaction is always when I make something beautiful and well-done that I can see on a real man or woman - not only in the glossy magazines.', '"Beautiful,Man,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402698', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', 'I don\'t like to treat a piece of clothing like an object of art because I don\'t consider myself an artist. I\'m a designer.', '"Art,Myself,Treat"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402699', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I inherited this collection of vinyl records, which at that time numbered 6,000, and I\'ve since continued to collect music. As you know, vinyl records can be very heavy, so every time I have to move into a new house, I need to build a complete new wall of shelves to put all these records, which is a nightmare for the architect."', '"Time,Music,New"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402700', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I always loved the look of musicians. I\'ve always admired them because they have a look - when I was growing up, it seemed that the ones I liked didn\'t need to have a stylist."', '"Look,Always,Loved"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402701', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I like tough relationships. I think relationships with conflict are good for you - you learn. But you can\'t listen too much. I have a strong point of view, and it\'s important that I fight for my ideas."', '"Good,Fight,View"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402702', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0c', '"I am comfortable giving people direction. If something is not good enough, my job is to find a way to help them learn from their mistake, and understand that next time I expect better."', '"Time,Good,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402703', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0d', '"Fragrance is, to me, something very personal; because it is something you wear every day, it should represent you and be an extension of your style."', '"Me,Style,Fragrance"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402704', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0d', '"I\'m obsessed with vinyasa flow yoga and Pilates. And since I live in Sweden, and we have good seafood, I tend to cook a lot of fish, preferably with oven-roasted veggies and a cauliflower mash."', '"Good,Fish,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402705', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0d', '"I try to be as organic and natural as possible when it comes to make up, so I always carry around coconut oil for removing and jojoba or Argan oil as a moisturiser."', '"Always,Possible,Organic"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402706', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0d', 'A Maybelline New York woman is strong and confident - I love that attitude.', '"Attitude,Love,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402707', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0d', 'I\'m honored and thrilled to represent such an iconic brand and to be a part of the Maybelline New York family.', '"Family,New,Honored"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402708', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"Feet, what do I need you for when I have wings to fly?"', '"Fly,Feet,Wings"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402709', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"There have been two great accidents in my life. One was the trolley, and the other was Diego. Diego was by far the worst."', '"Life,Great,My Life"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402710', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I tried to drown my sorrows, but the bastards learned how to swim, and now I am overwhelmed by this decent and good feeling."', '"Good,I Am,Drown"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402711', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I never paint dreams or nightmares. I paint my own reality.', '"Dreams,Reality,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402712', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I find that Americans completely lack sensibility and good taste. They are boring, and they all have faces like unbaked rolls."', '"Good,Boring,Find"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402713', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I am my own muse, the subject I know best."', '"Best,I Am,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402714', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I paint flowers so they will not die.', '"Die,Will,Flowers"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402715', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I leave you my portrait so that you will have my presence all the days and nights that I am away from you.', '"I Am,Portrait,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402716', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I paint self-portraits because I am so often alone, because I am the person I know best."', '"Alone,Best,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402717', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I paint my own reality. The only thing I know is that I paint because I need to, and I paint whatever passes through my head without any other consideration."', '"Reality,Know,My Own"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402718', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"The most important part of the body is the brain. Of my face, I like the eyebrows and eyes. Aside from that, I like nothing. My head is too small."', '"Eyes,Brain,Face"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402719', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"The only thing I know is that I paint because I need to, and I paint whatever passes through my head without any other consideration."', '"Know,Whatever,Paint"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402720', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I am happy to be alive, as long as I can paint."', '"I Am Happy,Long,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402721', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"They thought I was a Surrealist, but I wasn\'t. I never painted dreams. I painted my own reality."', '"Dreams,Reality,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402722', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I love you more than my own skin.', '"Love,Romantic,Skin"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402723', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'My painting carries with it the message of pain.', '"Pain,Painting,Message"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402724', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"Really, I do not know whether my paintings are surrealist or not, but I do know that they are the frankest expression of myself."', '"Myself,Know,Expression"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402725', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"I was a child who went about in a world of colors... My friends, my companions, became women slowly; I became old in instants."', '"Women,Colors,World"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402726', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'Painting completed my life.', '"Life,My Life,Painting"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402727', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"Of the opposite sex, I have the moustache and, in general, the face."', '"Sex,Face,Opposite"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402728', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I am in agreement with everything my father taught me and nothing my mother taught me.', '"Me,I Am,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402729', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"My toys were those of a boy: skates, bicycles."', '"Toys,Boy,Skates"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402730', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"Since my subjects have always been my sensations, my states of mind and the profound reactions that life has been producing in me, I have frequently objectified all this in figures of myself, which were the most sincere and real thing that I could do in order to express what I felt inside and outside of myself."', '"Life,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402731', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I don\'t know how to write love letters.', '"Love,Know,Letters"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402732', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', 'I put on the canvas whatever comes into my mind.', '"Mind,Canvas,Whatever"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402733', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0e', '"To paint is the most terrific thing that there is, but to do it well is very difficult."', '"Difficult,Paint,Well"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402734', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0f', 'Being rich and famous isn\'t all happiness and at times the pressures have got to me.', '"Happiness,Famous,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402735', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0f', 'I like to think of myself as being fashion-conscious without being a slave to fashion.', '"Myself,Fashion,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402736', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0f', 'Money cannot buy happiness.', '"Happiness,Money,Buy"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402737', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0f', 'I must have some sort of record in failing to get into the charts.', '"Must,Get,Some"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402738', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff0f', 'The kind of music I like depends very much on my mood.', '"Music,Mood,Depends"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402739', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', 'I demolish my bridges behind me - then there is no choice but forward.', '"Me,Choice,Behind"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402740', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', 'The difficult is what takes a little time; the impossible is what takes a little longer.', '"Time,Impossible,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402741', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', '"It is better to go skiing and think of God, than go to church and think of sport."', '"God,Better,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402742', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', 'Alas! Alas! Life is full of disappointments; as one reaches one ridge there is always another and a higher one beyond which blocks the view.', '"Life,View,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402743', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', 'Never keep a line of retreat: it is a wretched invention.', '"Never,Invention,Keep"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402744', '6110d4a59c759c204c24ff10', 'Never stop because you are afraid - you are never so likely to be wrong.', '"Never,Never Stop,Stop"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402745', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff13', '"Even in the investigations into direct production of calcium peroxide in an alkali melt with highly compressed oxygen, it was found to be necessary to bring the high-pressure gas into contact with the suspension of lime in caustic alkali melt by agitation or some other means of mixing."', '"Oxygen,Contact,Gas"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402746', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff13', '"As early as 1912, we worked on the problem of the hydrogenation of organic substances with the aid of highly compressed hydrogen."', '"Organic,Early,Problem"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402747', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff13', '"As early as 1910, Ludwig Landsberg had suggested that I should examine the problem of splitting heavy oils and oil residues into benzines."', '"Oil,Early,Problem"', '2023-05-29 12:11:00', '2023-05-29 12:11:00'),
	('402748', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Emotions have no place in business, unless you do business with them."', '"Business,Emotions,Place"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402749', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"So then learn to conquer your fear. This is the only art we have to master nowadays: to look at things without fear, and to fearlessly do right."', '"Art,Fear,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402750', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The world is bad but not without hope. It is only hopeless when you look at it from an ideal viewpoint.', '"Hope,Look,World"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402751', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The difference between humans and wild animals is that humans pray before they commit murder.', '"Wild,Difference,Animals"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402752', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The only remedy against hunger is reasonable birth control.', '"Control,Birth,Hunger"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402753', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Someone who is about to die does not mourn the dead.', '"Death,Dead,Die"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402754', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Today\'s Communism can survive only if it abandons the myth of an infallible party, if it continues to think, and if it becomes democratic."', '"Today,Communism,Survive"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402755', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"In a society which is structured the wrong way, piety has no effect."', '"Society,Way,Wrong"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402756', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Before anything else, we need a new age of Enlightenment. Our present political systems must relinquish their claims on truth, justice and freedom and have to replace them with the search for truth, justice, freedom and reason."', '"Freedom,Truth,Age"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402757', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Human life is beyond comprehension.', '"Life,Beyond,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402758', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"The art of the cuisine, when fully mastered, is the one human capability of which only good things can be said."', '"Good,Art,Good Things"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402759', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Revolutions demand enormous sacrifices and, at the same time, create a new need to change the world again."', '"Change,Time,World"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402760', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Truth is always a delusion.', '"Truth,Always,Delusion"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402761', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"A story is not finished, until it took the worst turn."', '"Worst,Story,Turn"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402762', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Man is imperfect. The reality he creates is always endangered by man.', '"Reality,Man,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402763', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"When death has you by the throat, you don\'t mince words."', '"Death,Words,Throat"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402764', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The rightful claim to dissent is an existential right of the individual.', '"Right,Dissent,Individual"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402765', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Nothing that has been thought can ever be taken back.', '"Nothing,Back,Thought"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402766', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Religion and political expediency go beautifully hand in hand.', '"Religion,Political,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402767', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'It is inhuman to continue a war which could easily be ended.', '"War,Continue,Inhuman"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402768', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The evolution of humans can not only be seen as the grand total of their wars; it is also defined by the evolution of the human mind and the development of the human consciousness.', '"Mind,Development,Evolution"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402769', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Resistance at all cost is the most senseless act there is.', '"Act,Resistance,Cost"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402770', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The freedom of each individual can only be the freedom of all.', '"Freedom,Only,Individual"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402771', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'For a person who is dying only eternity counts.', '"Person,Eternity,Dying"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402772', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'There are thoughts we must not think.', '"Thoughts,Think,Must"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402773', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Justice is horrible.', '"Justice,Horrible"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402774', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'World history is tragic.', '"History,World,World History"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402775', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The savages don\'t have atom bombs.', '"Bombs,Savages,Atom"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402776', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The problems of all of humanity can only be solved by all of humanity.', '"Humanity,Problems,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402777', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Everything in the world can be changed, my dear Florestan, but the human being."', '"World,Everything,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402778', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Above all, be suspicious of your fatherland. Nobody is more inclined to become a murderer than a fatherland."', '"Nobody,Your,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402779', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'We do not consider patriotism desirable if it contradicts civilized behavior.', '"Patriotism,Behavior,Consider"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402780', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'One does not set fire to a world which is already lost.', '"Fire,World,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402781', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'The worst possible turn can not be programmed. It is caused by coincidence.', '"Worst,Possible,Coincidence"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402782', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Today\'s difference between Russia and the United States is that in Russia everybody takes everybody else for a spy, and in the United States everybody takes everybody else for a criminal."', '"Today,Difference,Russia"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402783', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Whoever is content with the world, and who profits from its lack of justice, does not want to change it."', '"Change,Justice,World"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402784', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Our science has become terrible, our research dangerous, our findings deadly. We physicists have to make peace with reality. Reality is not as strong as we are. We will ruin reality."', '"Science,Peace,Reality"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402785', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"For people who have no critical acumen, a state is a mythical entity, for those who think critically it is a rational fiction, created by man in order to facilitate human coexistence."', '"Man,People,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402786', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'A major power can afford a military debacle only when it looks like a political victory.', '"Power,Political,Victory"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402787', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'A state always calls itself fatherland when it is ready for murder.', '"Always,Ready,State"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402788', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'A story has been thought through to the end when it has taken the worst possible turn.', '"End,Worst,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402789', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Only the freedom of mind can prevent the state from becoming totalitarian and from issuing totalitarian demands.', '"Freedom,Mind,State"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402790', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"News reports don\'t change the world. Only facts change it, and those have already happened when we get the news."', '"Change,World,Facts"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402791', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'There are risks which are not acceptable: the destruction of humanity is one of them.', '"Humanity,Risks,Destruction"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402792', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'It is surely easier to confess a murder over a cup of coffee than in front of a jury.', '"Coffee,Jury,Over"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402793', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'Power is paradoxical.', '"Power,Paradoxical"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402794', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'We are the world.', 'World', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402795', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Who sows fear, reaps weapons."', '"Fear,Who,Weapons"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402796', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'You can\'t take back an act you were able to think.', '"Back,Act,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402797', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'It is easy to kill when you don\'t see your victim.', '"See,Easy,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402798', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"I am a man, and God is hiding from us humans. We are unable to see Him, we can only search for Him."', '"God,Man,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402799', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'People like us who are on their last leg can only understand comedies.', '"People,Understand,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402800', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"There is a moment when nothing can be wiped out and left behind any more, when there is only reality and reality is horrifying."', '"Moment,Reality,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402801', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', 'This inhuman world has to become more humane. But how?', '"World,More,Become"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402802', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Pretend to be dumb, that\'s the only way to reach old age."', '"Age,Old Age,Dumb"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402803', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Communism is a proposition to structure the world more reasonably, a proposition for changing the world. As such, we have to analyze it and, if we deem it reasonable, act upon it."', '"World,Communism,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402804', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Without tolerance, our world turns into hell."', '"World,Hell,Tolerance"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402805', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff14', '"Everything that is necessary is also easy. You just have to accept it. And the most necessary, the most natural matter on this planet is death."', '"Death,Accept,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402806', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff15', '"Without democracy there is no freedom. Violence, no matter who is using it, is always reactionary."', '"Freedom,Democracy,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402807', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff15', 'Freedom and Justice are twin sisters.', '"Freedom,Justice,Sisters"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402808', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff15', '"Thus we have at least a national song that unites all Germans, and is the symbol of our sixty-million nation."', '"Song,Nation,National"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402809', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', 'Freedom is the recognition of necessity.', '"Freedom,Recognition,Necessity"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402810', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', 'All history has been a history of class struggles between dominated classes at various stages of social development.', '"History,Development,Social"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402811', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', 'The state is nothing but an instrument of opression of one class by another - no less so in a democratic republic than in a monarchy.', '"Nothing,Monarchy,State"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402812', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', '"Just as Darwin discovered the law of development of organic nature, so Marx discovered the law of development of human history: the simple fact, hitherto concealed by an overgrowth of ideology, that mankind must first of all eat, drink, have shelter and clothing, before it can pursue politics, science, art, religion, etc."', '"Nature,Politics,Science"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402813', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', '"From the first day to this, sheer greed was the driving spirit of civilization."', '"Day,Greed,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402814', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', '"Everything must justify its existence before the judgment seat of Reason, or give up existence."', '"Everything,Reason,Existence"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402815', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', '"The state is not abolished, it withers away."', '"State,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402816', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', '"The proletariat uses the State not in the interests of freedom but in order to hold down its adversaries, and as soon as it becomes possible to speak of freedom the State as such ceases to exist."', '"Freedom,Speak,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402817', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', 'Some laws of state aimed at curbing crime are even more criminal.', '"More,State,Laws"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402818', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff16', 'Look at the Paris Commune. That was the Dictatorship of the Proletariat.', '"Look,Dictatorship,Proletariat"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402819', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"Industry entirely left to itself, would soon fall to ruin, and a nation letting everything alone would commit suicide."', '"Alone,Suicide,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402820', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"But the general welfare must restrict and regulate the exertions of the individuals, as the individuals must derive a supply of their strength from social power."', '"Strength,Power,Welfare"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402821', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"An individual, in promoting his own interest, may injure the public interest; a nation, in promoting the general welfare, may check the interest of a part of its members."', '"Own,Welfare,Nation"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402822', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', 'It is bad policy to regulate everything... where things may better regulate themselves and can be better promoted by private exertions; but it is no less bad policy to let those things alone which can only be promoted by interfering social power.', '"Alone,Power,Government"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402823', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"Look around, and you see everywhere the exertions and acts of individuals restricted, regulated, or promoted, on the principle of the common welfare."', '"Look,See,Welfare"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402824', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"Only now did I recognize the reciprocal relationship which exits between manufacturing power and the national system of transportation, and that the one can never develop to its fullest without the other."', '"Relationship,Power,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402825', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"The concentration and reciprocal effect of industry and agriculture conjoin in a growth of productive powers, which increases more in geometrical than in arithmetical proportion."', '"Growth,Agriculture,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402826', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"The more a person learns how to use the forces of nature for his own purposes, by means of perfecting the sciences and the invention and improvement of machines, the more he will produce."', '"Nature,Improvement,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402827', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff19', '"The relationship I have to my fatherland is like that of mothers with crippled children: they love them all the more, the more crippled they are. Germany is the background of all my plans, the return to Germany."', '"Love,Relationship,Children"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402828', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'He who has a why to live can bear almost any how.', '"Life,Live,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402829', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Whoever fights monsters should see to it that in the process he does not become a monster. And if you gaze long enough into an abyss, the abyss will gaze back into you."', '"Long,Process,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402830', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"To live is to suffer, to survive is to find some meaning in the suffering."', '"Suffering,Live,Survive"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402831', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'That which does not kill us makes us stronger.', '"Strength,Stronger,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402832', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'One must still have chaos in oneself to be able to give birth to a dancing star.', '"Chaos,Birth,Able"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402833', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Hope in reality is the worst of all evils because it prolongs the torments of man.', '"Hope,Reality,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402834', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'He who would learn to fly one day must first learn to stand and walk and run and climb and dance; one cannot fly into flying.', '"Learning,Walk,Fly"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402835', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"We love life, not because we are used to living but because we are used to loving."', '"Life,Love,Love Life"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402836', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Without music, life would be a mistake."', '"Life,Music,Mistake"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402837', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"It is not a lack of love, but a lack of friendship that makes unhappy marriages."', '"Friendship,Love,Marriage"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402838', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'We should consider every day lost on which we have not danced at least once. And we should call every truth false which was not accompanied by at least one laugh.', '"Truth,Day,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402839', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The true man wants two things: danger and play. For that reason he wants woman, as the most dangerous plaything."', '"Man,Woman,True"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402840', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is always some madness in love. But there is also always some reason in madness.', '"Love,Relationship,Madness"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402841', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are no facts, only interpretations."', '"Truth,Facts,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402842', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"When you look into an abyss, the abyss also looks into you."', '"Look,Abyss,Looks"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402843', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"God is dead. God remains dead. And we have killed him. Yet his shadow still looms. How shall we comfort ourselves, the murderers of all murderers? What was holiest and mightiest of all that the world has yet owned has bled to death under our knives; who will wipe this blood off us? What water is there for us to clean ourselves?"', '"God,Death,Water"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402844', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is more wisdom in your body than in your deepest philosophy.', '"Wisdom,Body,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402845', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'All things are subject to interpretation whichever interpretation prevails at a given time is a function of power and not truth.', '"Truth,Time,Power"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402846', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The future influences the present just as much as the past.', '"Future,Past,Present"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402847', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In individuals, insanity is rare; but in groups, parties, nations and epochs, it is the rule."', '"Rare,Insanity,Rule"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402848', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'In every real man a child is hidden that wants to play.', '"Man,Real Man,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402849', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The man of knowledge must be able not only to love his enemies but also to hate his friends.', '"Love,Wisdom,Knowledge"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402850', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Madness is rare in individuals - but in groups, parties, nations, and ages it is the rule."', '"Madness,Rare,Rule"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402851', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"You have your way. I have my way. As for the right way, the correct way, and the only way, it does not exist."', '"Way,Right,Your"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402852', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"On the mountains of truth you can never climb in vain: either you will reach a point higher up today, or you will be training your powers so that you will be able to climb higher tomorrow."', '"Truth,Today,Tomorrow"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402853', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'All truly great thoughts are conceived by walking.', '"Great,Thoughts,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402854', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Thoughts are the shadows of our feelings - always darker, emptier and simpler."', '"Thoughts,Feelings,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402855', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The essence of all beautiful art, all great art, is gratitude."', '"Art,Great,Beautiful"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402856', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The irrationality of a thing is no argument against its existence, rather a condition of it."', '"Argument,Existence,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402857', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'It is impossible to suffer without making someone pay for it; every complaint already contains revenge.', '"Revenge,Impossible,Someone"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402858', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In heaven, all the interesting people are missing."', '"People,Heaven,Missing"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402859', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Faith: not wanting to know what is true.', '"Faith,True,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402860', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Ah, women. They make the highs higher and the lows more frequent."', '"Women,More,Lows"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402861', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Blessed are the forgetful: for they get the better even of their blunders.', '"Blessed,Better,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402862', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Convictions are more dangerous foes of truth than lies.', '"Truth,Dangerous,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402863', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A casual stroll through the lunatic asylum shows that faith does not prove anything.', '"Faith,Anything,Casual"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402864', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The surest way to corrupt a youth is to instruct him to hold in higher esteem those who think alike than those who think differently.', '"Youth,Way,Think"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402865', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Woman was God\'s second mistake.', '"God,Mistake,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402866', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There cannot be a God because if there were one, I could not believe that I was not He."', '"God,Believe,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402867', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The doer alone learneth.', '"Alone,Graduation,Doer"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402868', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Perhaps I know best why it is man alone who laughs; he alone suffers so deeply that he had to invent laughter.', '"Alone,Best,Laughter"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402869', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The best weapon against an enemy is another enemy.', '"Best,War,Enemy"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402870', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"When one has not had a good father, one must create one."', '"Good,Dad,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402871', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'We have art in order not to die of the truth.', '"Truth,Art,Die"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402872', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Many are stubborn in pursuit of the path they have chosen, few in pursuit of the goal."', '"Path,Stubborn,Chosen"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402873', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Love is blind; friendship closes its eyes.', '"Friendship,Love,Eyes"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402874', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The most common lie is that which one lies to himself; lying to others is relatively an exception.', '"Lie,Others,Lies"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402875', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Women are considered deep - why? Because one can never discover any bottom to them. Women are not even shallow.', '"Women,Never,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402876', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whatever is done for love always occurs beyond good and evil.', '"Love,Good,Good And Evil"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402877', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whenever I climb I am followed by a dog called \'Ego\'.', '"I Am,Ego,Dog"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402878', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Let us beware of saying that death is the opposite of life. The living being is only a species of the dead, and a very rare species."', '"Life,Death,Dead"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402879', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Insanity in individuals is something rare - but in groups, parties, nations and epochs, it is the rule."', '"Rare,Insanity,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402880', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'One should die proudly when it is no longer possible to live proudly.', '"Die,Live,Possible"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402881', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Fear is the mother of morality.', '"Fear,Morality,Mother"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402882', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'To forget one\'s purpose is the commonest form of stupidity.', '"Stupidity,Purpose,Forget"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402883', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"For the woman, the man is a means: the end is always the child."', '"Man,Woman,End"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402884', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"When marrying, ask yourself this question: Do you believe that you will be able to converse well with this person into your old age? Everything else in marriage is transitory."', '"Age,Marriage,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402885', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'It is my ambition to say in ten sentences what others say in a whole book.', '"Ambition,Others,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402886', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"A woman may very well form a friendship with a man, but for this to endure, it must be assisted by a little physical antipathy."', '"Friendship,Man,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402887', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'We often refuse to accept an idea merely because the tone of voice in which it has been expressed is unsympathetic to us.', '"Accept,Voice,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402888', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Those who cannot understand how to put their thoughts on ice should not enter into the heat of debate.', '"Thoughts,Heat,Debate"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402889', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'What is great in man is that he is a bridge and not a goal.', '"Great,Man,Bridge"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402890', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are various eyes. Even the Sphinx has eyes: and as a result there are various truths, and as a result there is no truth."', '"Truth,Eyes,Result"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402891', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'I cannot believe in a God who wants to be praised all the time.', '"God,Time,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402892', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Not necessity, not desire - no, the love of power is the demon of men. Let them have everything - health, food, a place to live, entertainment - they are and remain unhappy and low-spirited: for the demon waits and waits and will be satisfied."', '"Love,Health,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402893', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Talking much about oneself can also be a means to conceal oneself.', '"Talking,About,Oneself"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402894', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Morality is the herd-instinct in the individual.', '"Morality,Individual"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402895', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whoever despises himself nonetheless respects himself as one who despises.', '"Who,Himself,Nonetheless"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402896', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'After coming into contact with a religious man I always feel I must wash my hands.', '"Man,Feel,Hands"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402897', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The world itself is the will to power - and nothing else! And you yourself are the will to power - and nothing else!', '"Power,World,Yourself"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402898', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The great epochs of our life are the occasions when we gain the courage to rebaptize our evil qualities as our best qualities.', '"Life,Best,Courage"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402899', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Sleeping is no mean art: for its sake one must stay awake all day.', '"Art,Day,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402900', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '\'Evil men have no songs.\' How is it that the Russians have songs?', '"Men,Evil,How"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402901', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Egoism is the very essence of a noble soul.', '"Soul,Noble,Essence"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402902', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Our treasure lies in the beehive of our knowledge. We are perpetually on the way thither, being by nature winged insects and honey gatherers of the mind."', '"Nature,Knowledge,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402903', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'All truth is simple... is that not doubly a lie?', '"Truth,Simple,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402904', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A pair of powerful spectacles has sometimes sufficed to cure a person in love.', '"Love,Sometimes,Person"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402905', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The demand to be loved is the greatest of all arrogant presumptions.', '"Great,Loved,Demand"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402906', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'I would believe only in a God that knows how to Dance.', '"God,Believe,Dance"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402907', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Wit is the epitaph of an emotion.', '"Emotion,Wit,Epitaph"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402908', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Stupid as a man, say the women: cowardly as a woman, say the men. Stupidity in a woman is unwomanly."', '"Women,Men,Stupid"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402909', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Is life not a thousand times too short for us to bore ourselves?', '"Life,Us,Short"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402910', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'One has to pay dearly for immortality; one has to die several times while one is still alive.', '"Die,Alive,Immortality"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402911', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'War has always been the grand sagacity of every spirit which has grown too inward and too profound; its curative power lies even in the wounds one receives.', '"War,Power,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402912', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"One ought to hold on to one\'s heart; for if one lets it go, one soon loses control of the head too."', '"Heart,Control,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402913', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In large states public education will always be mediocre, for the same reason that in large kitchens the cooking is usually bad."', '"Education,Cooking,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402914', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are no eternal facts, as there are no absolute truths."', '"Facts,Eternal,Absolute"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402915', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"I assess the power of a will by how much resistance, pain, torture it endures and knows how to turn to its advantage."', '"Power,Pain,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402916', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Nothing is beautiful, only man: on this piece of naivete rests all aesthetics, it is the first truth of aesthetics. Let us immediately add its second: nothing is ugly but degenerate man - the domain of aesthetic judgment is therewith defined."', '"Truth,Beautiful,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402917', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There is an innocence in admiration; it is found in those to whom it has never yet occurred that they, too, might be admired some day."', '"Day,Innocence,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402918', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"One may sometimes tell a lie, but the grimace that accompanies it tells the truth."', '"Truth,Lie,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402919', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Behind all their personal vanity, women themselves always have an impersonal contempt for woman."', '"Women,Woman,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402920', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Go up close to your friend, but do not go over to him! We should also respect the enemy in our friend."', '"Respect,Enemy,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402921', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"If there is something to pardon in everything, there is also something to condemn."', '"Forgiveness,Everything,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402922', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"When a hundred men stand together, each of them loses his mind and gets another one."', '"Men,Together,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402923', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"All credibility, all good conscience, all evidence of truth come only from the senses."', '"Truth,Good,Conscience"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402924', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'It is always consoling to think of suicide: in that way one gets through many a bad night.', '"Night,Suicide,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402925', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are horrible people who, instead of solving a problem, tangle it up and make it harder to solve for anyone who wants to deal with it. Whoever does not know how to hit the nail on the head should be asked not to hit it at all."', '"People,Know,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402926', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Art is the proper task of life.', '"Life,Art,Task"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402927', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Arrogance on the part of the meritorious is even more offensive to us than the arrogance of those without merit: for merit itself is offensive.', '"Arrogance,More,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402928', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"What really raises one\'s indignation against suffering is not suffering intrinsically, but the senselessness of suffering."', '"Suffering,Against,Really"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402929', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The \'kingdom of Heaven\' is a condition of the heart - not something that comes \'upon the earth\' or \'after death.\'', '"Death,Heart,Earth"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402930', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'No one lies so boldly as the man who is indignant.', '"Man,Who,Lies"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402931', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is not enough religion in the world even to destroy religion.', '"Religion,World,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402932', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Words are but symbols for the relations of things to one another and to us; nowhere do they touch upon absolute truth.', '"Truth,Words,Touch"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402933', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"What? You seek something? You wish to multiply yourself tenfold, a hundredfold? You seek followers? Seek zeros!"', '"Yourself,Wish,Followers"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402934', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'He who cannot give anything away cannot feel anything either.', '"Feel,Anything,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402935', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"For art to exist, for any sort of aesthetic activity to exist, a certain physiological precondition is indispensable: intoxication."', '"Art,Aesthetic,Activity"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402936', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Success has always been a great liar.', '"Success,Great,Liar"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402937', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"I still live, I still think: I still have to live, for I still have to think."', '"Live,Think,Still"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402938', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'He that humbleth himself wishes to be exalted.', '"Wishes,He,Himself"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402939', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"When one has finished building one\'s house, one suddenly realizes that in the process one has learned something that one really needed to know in the worst way - before one began."', '"Process,Way,Building"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402940', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Art raises its head where creeds relax.', '"Art,Relax,Head"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402941', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Love is not consolation. It is light.', '"Love,Love Is,Light"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402942', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'He who fights with monsters might take care lest he thereby become a monster. Is not life a hundred times too short for us to bore ourselves?', '"Life,Care,Take Care"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402943', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are no moral phenomena at all, but only a moral interpretation of phenomena."', '"Moral,Only,Interpretation"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402944', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'In Christianity neither morality nor religion come into contact with reality at any point.', '"Religion,Reality,Morality"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402945', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"What is good? All that heightens the feeling of power, the will to power, power itself in man."', '"Good,Power,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402946', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'When one has a great deal to put into it a day has a hundred pockets.', '"Great,Day,Deal"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402947', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Anyone who has declared someone else to be an idiot, a bad apple, is annoyed when it turns out in the end that he isn\'t."', '"Bad,Idiot,End"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402948', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Shared joys make a friend, not shared sufferings."', '"Friend,Make,Sufferings"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402949', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Germany is a great nation only because its people have so much Polish blood in their veins.', '"Great,People,Blood"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402950', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Glance into the world just as though time were gone: and everything crooked will become straight to you.', '"Time,World,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402951', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'In music the passions enjoy themselves.', '"Music,Enjoy,Themselves"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402952', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is not enough love and goodness in the world to permit giving any of it away to imaginary beings.', '"Love,World,Enough"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402953', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Do whatever you will, but first be such as are able to will."', '"Will,Whatever,First"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402954', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Although the most acute judges of the witches and even the witches themselves, were convinced of the guilt of witchery, the guilt nevertheless was non-existent. It is thus with all guilt."', '"Guilt,Judges,Witches"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402955', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Art is not merely an imitation of the reality of nature, but in truth a metaphysical supplement to the reality of nature, placed alongside thereof for its conquest."', '"Nature,Truth,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402956', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"This is the hardest of all: to close the open hand out of love, and keep modest as a giver."', '"Love,Open,Hardest"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402957', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The abdomen is the reason why man does not readily take himself to be a god.', '"God,Man,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402958', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"It is not when truth is dirty, but when it is shallow, that the lover of knowledge is reluctant to step into its waters."', '"Truth,Knowledge,Step"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402959', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Does wisdom perhaps appear on the earth as a raven which is inspired by the smell of carrion?', '"Wisdom,Earth,Smell"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402960', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In the consciousness of the truth he has perceived, man now sees everywhere only the awfulness or the absurdity of existence and loathing seizes him."', '"Truth,Man,Consciousness"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402961', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Regarding life, the wisest men of all ages have judged alike: it is worthless."', '"Life,Men,Worthless"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402962', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'I love those who do not know how to live for today.', '"Love,Today,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402963', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Idleness is the parent of psychology.', '"Parent,Idleness,Psychology"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402964', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'I am a pure-blooded Polish nobleman without a single drop of bad blood - certainly not German blood.', '"I Am,Bad,Blood"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402965', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Love matches, so called, have illusion for their father and need for their mother."', '"Love,Illusion,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402966', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Our vanity is hardest to wound precisely when our pride has just been wounded.', '"Pride,Hardest,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402967', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Rejoicing in our joy, not suffering over our suffering, makes someone a friend."', '"Friendship,Joy,Suffering"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402968', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There are slavish souls who carry their appreciation for favors done them so far that they strangle themselves with the rope of gratitude.', '"Appreciation,Gratitude,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402969', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'If a woman possesses manly virtues one should run away from her; and if she does not possess them she runs away from herself.', '"Woman,Virtues,She"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402970', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Mystical explanations are thought to be deep; the truth is that they are not even shallow.', '"Truth,Deep,Truth Is"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402971', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Is Wagner a human being at all? Is he not rather a disease? He contaminates everything he touches - he has made music sick.', '"Music,Everything,Disease"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402972', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Judgments, value judgments concerning life, for or against, can in the last resort never be true: they possess value only as symptoms, they come into consideration only as symptoms - in themselves such judgments are stupidities."', '"Life,Value,True"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402973', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"People who have given us their complete confidence believe that they have a right to ours. The inference is false, a gift confers no rights."', '"Confidence,Believe,Gift"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402974', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Existence really is an imperfect tense that never becomes a present.', '"Never,Present,Existence"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402975', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In the last analysis, even the best man is evil: in the last analysis, even the best woman is bad."', '"Best,Man,Woman"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402976', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"I do not know what the spirit of a philosopher could more wish to be than a good dancer. For the dance is his ideal, also his fine art, finally also the only kind of piety he knows, his \'divine service.\'"', '"Good,Art,Service"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402977', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Is man one of God\'s blunders? Or is God one of man\'s blunders?', '"God,Man,Blunders"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402978', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"He who laughs best today, will also laughs last."', '"Best,Today,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402979', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Character is determined more by the lack of certain experiences than by those one has had.', '"Character,More,Had"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402980', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Once spirit was God, then it became man, and now it is even becoming mob."', '"God,Man,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402981', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The word \'Christianity\' is already a misunderstanding - in reality there has been only one Christian, and he died on the Cross."', '"Reality,Misunderstanding,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402982', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The aphorism in which I am the first master among Germans, are the forms of \'eternity\'; my ambition is to say in ten sentences what everyone else says in a book - what everyone else does not say in a book."', '"I Am,Ambition,Everyone"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402983', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A subject for a great poet would be God\'s boredom after the seventh day of creation.', '"God,Great,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402984', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The Christian resolution to find the world ugly and bad has made the world ugly and bad.', '"World,Bad,Ugly"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402985', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'In everything one thing is impossible: rationality.', '"Impossible,Everything,One Thing"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402986', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Admiration for a quality or an art can be so strong that it deters us from striving to possess it.', '"Art,Quality,Strong"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402987', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'It is the most sensual men who need to flee women and torment their bodies.', '"Women,Men,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402988', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Many a man fails as an original thinker simply because his memory it too good.', '"Good,Man,Memory"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402989', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Great indebtedness does not make men grateful, but vengeful; and if a little charity is not forgotten, it turns into a gnawing worm."', '"Men,Great,Grateful"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402990', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'We hear only those questions for which we are in a position to find answers.', '"Questions,Find,Position"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402991', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'God is a thought who makes crooked all that is straight.', '"God,Religion,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402992', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'One often contradicts an opinion when what is uncongenial is really the tone in which it was conveyed.', '"Opinion,Often,Tone"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402993', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'In praise there is more obtrusiveness than in blame.', '"Praise,Blame,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402994', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Every church is a stone on the grave of a god-man: it does not want him to rise up again under any circumstances.', '"Stone,Rise,Church"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402995', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'At times one remains faithful to a cause only because its opponents do not cease to be insipid.', '"Faithful,Because,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402996', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Today I love myself as I love my god: who could charge me with a sin today? I know only sins against my god; but who knows my god?', '"Love,God,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402997', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"It is good to express a thing twice right at the outset and so to give it a right foot and also a left one. Truth can surely stand on one leg, but with two it will be able to walk and get around."', '"Truth,Good,Walk"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402998', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'What do you regard as most humane? To spare someone shame.', '"Someone,Shame,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('402999', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'You say it is the good cause that hallows even war? I say unto you: it is the good war that hallows any cause.', '"War,Good,Say"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403000', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"We do not hate as long as we still attach a lesser value, but only when we attach an equal or a greater value."', '"Hate,Long,Value"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403001', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Whoever has provoked men to rage against him has always gained a party in his favor, too."', '"Men,Always,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403002', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The lie is a condition of life.', '"Life,Lie,Condition"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403003', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The press, the machine, the railway, the telegraph are premises whose thousand-year conclusion no one has yet dared to draw."', '"Railway,Conclusion,Press"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403004', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Experience, as a desire for experience, does not come off. We must not study ourselves while having an experience."', '"Experience,Desire,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403005', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'An artist has no home in Europe except in Paris.', '"Home,Europe,Artist"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403006', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"What do I care about the purring of one who cannot love, like the cat?"', '"Love,Care,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403007', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"What can everyone do? Praise and blame. This is human virtue, this is human madness."', '"Praise,Blame,Madness"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403008', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'And we should consider every day lost on which we have not danced at least once. And we should call every truth false which was not accompanied by at least one laugh.', '"Truth,Day,Lost"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403009', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Necessity is not an established fact, but an interpretation."', '"Necessity,Interpretation,Fact"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403010', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'The best author will be the one who is ashamed to become a writer.', '"Best,Will,Ashamed"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403011', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whoever does not have a good father should procure one.', '"Good,Dad,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403012', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'This is what is hardest: to close the open hand because one loves.', '"Open,Hardest,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403013', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A good writer possesses not only his own spirit but also the spirit of his friends.', '"Good,Spirit,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403014', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"In the course of history, men come to see that iron necessity is neither iron nor necessary."', '"History,Men,See"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403015', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'To use the same words is not a sufficient guarantee of understanding; one must use the same words for the same genus of inward experience; ultimately one must have one\'s experiences in common.', '"Experience,Words,Understanding"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403016', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'To be ashamed of one\'s immorality: that is a step on the staircase at whose end one is also ashamed of one\'s morality.', '"Step,End,Morality"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403017', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Before the effect one believes in different causes than one does after the effect.', '"After,Before,Different"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403018', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Extreme positions are not succeeded by moderate ones, but by contrary extreme positions."', '"Extreme,Moderate,Succeeded"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403019', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Every man is a creative cause of what happens, a primum mobile with an original movement."', '"Man,Happens,Movement"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403020', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Fanatics are picturesque, mankind would rather see gestures than listen to reasons."', '"See,Rather,Gestures"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403021', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'When art dresses in worn-out material it is most easily recognized as art.', '"Art,Dresses,Most"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403022', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The desire to annoy no one, to harm no one, can equally well be the sign of a just as of an anxious disposition."', '"Desire,Well,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403023', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is a rollicking kindness that looks like malice.', '"Kindness,Looks,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403024', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'It says nothing against the ripeness of a spirit that it has a few worms.', '"Nothing,Spirit,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403025', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"The bad gains respect through imitation, the good loses it especially in art."', '"Respect,Good,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403026', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Sing me a new song; the world is transfigured; all the Heavens are rejoicing.', '"Me,World,Song"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403027', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'When one does away with oneself one does the most estimable thing possible: one thereby almost deserves to live.', '"Live,Possible,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403028', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Of all that is written, I love only what a person has written with his own blood."', '"Love,Person,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403029', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"All sciences are now under the obligation to prepare the ground for the future task of the philosopher, which is to solve the problem of value, to determine the true hierarchy of values."', '"Future,Value,True"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403030', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Not when truth is dirty, but when it is shallow, does the enlightened man dislike to wade into its waters."', '"Truth,Man,Dirty"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403031', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"There are people who want to make men\'s lives more difficult for no other reason than the chance it provides them afterwards to offer their prescription for alleviating life; their Christianity, for instance."', '"Life,Men,Chance"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403032', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whoever has witnessed another\'s ideal becomes his inexorable judge and as it were his evil conscience.', '"Evil,Conscience,Judge"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403033', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is in general good reason to suppose that in several respects the gods could all benefit from instruction by us human beings. We humans are - more humane.', '"Good,Reason,More"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403034', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Whoever feels predestined to see and not to believe will find all believers too noisy and pushy: he guards against them.', '"Believe,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403035', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Some are made modest by great praise, others insolent."', '"Great,Praise,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403036', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Plato was a bore.', 'Bore', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403037', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A friend should be a master at guessing and keeping still: you must not want to see everything.', '"See,Everything,Master"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403038', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Nothing has been purchased more dearly than the little bit of reason and sense of freedom which now constitutes our pride.', '"Freedom,Pride,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403039', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'Genteel women suppose that those things do not really exist about which it is impossible to talk in polite company.', '"Women,Impossible,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403040', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'A great value of antiquity lies in the fact that its writings are the only ones that modern men still read with exactness.', '"Men,Great,Value"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403041', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', '"Undeserved praise causes more pangs of conscience later than undeserved blame, but probably only for this reason, that our power of judgment are more completely exposed by being over praised than by being unjustly underestimated."', '"Power,Praise,Blame"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403042', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'What then in the last resort are the truths of mankind? They are the irrefutable errors of mankind.', '"Last,Errors,Mankind"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403043', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1a', 'There is nothing we like to communicate to others as much as the seal of secrecy together with what lies under it.', '"Together,Nothing,Others"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403044', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Against stupidity the very gods themselves contend in vain.', '"Stupidity,Gods,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403045', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The strong man is strongest when alone.', '"Alone,Man,Strong Man"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403046', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Keep true to the dreams of your youth.', '"Dreams,Teen,Youth"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403047', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The rich become richer and the poor become poorer is a cry heard throughout the whole civilized world.', '"World,Rich,Poor"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403048', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Grace is the beauty of form under the influence of freedom.', '"Inspirational,Beauty,Freedom"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403049', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Disappointments are to the soul what a thunderstorm is to the air.', '"Soul,Air,Thunderstorm"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403050', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Dare to err and to dream. Deep meaning often lies in childish plays.', '"Childish,Dare,Meaning"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403051', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Lose not yourself in a far off time, seize the moment that is thine."', '"Time,Moment,Lose"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403052', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"A merely fallen enemy may rise again, but the reconciled one is truly vanquished."', '"Rise,Enemy,May"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403053', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Happy he who learns to bear what he cannot change.', '"Happiness,Change,Happy"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403054', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Who dares nothing, need hope for nothing."', '"Hope,Nothing,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403055', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'That which is so universal as death must be a benefit.', '"Death,Universal,Must"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403056', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The history of the world is the world\'s court of justice.', '"History,Justice,World"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403057', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The voice of the majority is no proof of justice.', '"Justice,Voice,Proof"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403058', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Great souls suffer in silence.', '"Great,Silence,Suffer"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403059', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Live with your century; but do not be its creature.', '"Live,Your,Century"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403060', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Man only plays when in the full meaning of the word he is a man, and he is only completely a man when he plays."', '"Man,Meaning,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403061', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Art is the daughter of freedom.', '"Freedom,Art,Daughter"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403062', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'He who has done his best for his own time has lived for all times.', '"Best,Time,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403063', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Every true genius is bound to be naive.', '"Intelligence,True,Genius"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403064', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'A gloomy guest fits not a wedding feast.', '"Wedding,Feast,Gloomy"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403065', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'With stupidity the gods themselves struggle in vain.', '"Struggle,Stupidity,Gods"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403066', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Art is the right hand of Nature. The latter has only given us being, the former has made us men."', '"Nature,Men,Art"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403067', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"It is criminal to steal a purse, daring to steal a fortune, a mark of greatness to steal a crown. The blame diminishes as the guilt increases."', '"Greatness,Blame,Crown"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403068', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The will of man is his happiness.', '"Happiness,Man,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403069', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Honesty prospers in every condition of life.', '"Life,Honesty,Condition"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403070', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"To gain a crown by fighting is great, to reject it divine."', '"Great,Fighting,Crown"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403071', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'There is no such thing as chance; and what seem to us merest accident springs from the deepest source of destiny.', '"Chance,Destiny,Us"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403072', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'A noble heart will always capitulate to reason.', '"Heart,Will,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403073', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Revenge is barren of itself: it is the dreadful food it feeds on; its delight is murder, and its end is despair."', '"Food,Revenge,End"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403074', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Appearance rules the world.', '"World,Rules,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403075', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The universe is one of God\'s thoughts.', '"God,Thoughts,Universe"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403076', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Freedom can occur only through education.', '"Education,Freedom,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403077', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Utility is the great idol of the age, to which all powers must do service and all talents swear allegiance."', '"Age,Great,Service"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403078', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"In the society, where people are just parts in a larger machine, individuals are unable to develop fully."', '"Society,People,Develop"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403079', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The key to education is the experience of beauty.', '"Beauty,Education,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403080', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Nothing leads to good that is not natural.', '"Good,Nothing,Natural"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403081', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'It does not prove a thing to be right because the majority say it is so.', '"Right,Prove,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403082', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Votes should be weighed not counted.', '"Should,Counted,Weighed"', '2023-05-29 12:12:00', '2023-05-29 12:12:00'),
	('403083', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"The greater part of humanity is too much harassed and fatigued by the struggle with want, to rally itself for a new and sterner struggle with error."', '"Struggle,Humanity,New"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403084', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'It is easy to give advice from a port of safety.', '"Advice,Safety,Easy"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403085', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Power is the most persuasive rhetoric.', '"Power,Persuasive,Rhetoric"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403086', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Peace is rarely denied to the peaceful.', '"Peace,Denied,Peaceful"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403087', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Mankind is made great or little by its own will.', '"Inspirational,Great,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403088', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'There is room in the smallest cottage for a happy loving pair.', '"Love,Happy,Room"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403089', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The jest loses its point when he who makes it is the first to laugh.', '"Laugh,Point,First"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403090', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'All things must; man is the only creature that wills.', '"Man,Things,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403091', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Of all the possessions of this life fame is the noblest; when the body has sunk into the dust the great name still lives.', '"Life,Great,Body"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403092', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'He who considers too much will perform little.', '"Will,Too Much,He"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403093', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Be noble minded! Our own heart, and not other men\'s opinions of us, forms our true honor."', '"Men,Heart,Honor"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403094', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Posterity weaves no garlands for imitators.', '"Posterity,Imitators"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403095', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Aesthetic matters are fundamental for the harmonious development of both society and the individual.', '"Society,Development,Aesthetic"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403096', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'It hinders the creative work of the mind if the intellect examines too closely the ideas as they pour in.', '"Work,Mind,Ideas"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403097', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'I am better than my reputation.', '"I Am,Better,Reputation"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403098', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Opposition always inflames the enthusiast, never converts him."', '"Never,Always,Opposition"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403099', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"No doubt the artist is the child of his time; but woe to him if he is also its disciple, or even its favorite."', '"Time,Doubt,Child"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403100', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'It is often wise to reveal that which cannot be concealed for long.', '"Wise,Long,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403101', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Knowledge, the object of knowledge and the knower are the three factors which motivate action; the senses, the work and the doer comprise the threefold basis of action."', '"Work,Knowledge,Action"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403102', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"They would need to be already wise, in order to love wisdom."', '"Love,Wisdom,Wise"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403103', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Not without a shudder may the human hand reach into the mysterious urn of destiny.', '"Destiny,Mysterious,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403104', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Full of wisdom are the ordinations of fate.', '"Wisdom,Fate,Full"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403105', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'Worthless is the nation that does not gladly stake its all on its honor.', '"Honor,Nation,Worthless"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403106', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'No emperor has the power to dictate to the heart.', '"Power,Heart,Emperor"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403107', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'The world is ruled only by consideration of advantages.', '"World,Only,Consideration"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403108', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'To save all we must risk all.', '"Save,Risk,Must"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403109', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"Will it, and set to work briskly."', '"Work,Will,Set"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403110', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', 'It is difficult to discriminate the voice of truth from amid the clamor raised by heated partisans.', '"Truth,Difficult,Voice"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403111', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1c', '"As freely as the firmament embraces the world, or the sun pours forth impartially his beams, so mercy must encircle both friend and foe."', '"World,Sun,Mercy"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403112', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', 'The essence of religion consists in the feeling of an absolute dependence.', '"Religion,Feeling,Essence"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403113', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', '"And, moreover, it is art in its most general and comprehensive form that is here discussed, for the dialogue embraces everything connected with it, from its greatest object, the state, to its least, the embellishment of sensuous existence."', '"Art,Everything,Connected"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403114', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', '"The first, that their pretensions to this possession of an art properly so called in their art of speaking are entirely unfounded; and the second, that they are involved in a profound mistake in their confusion of the good with the pleasant."', '"Good,Art,Mistake"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403115', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', '"For when it is the good that is under consideration, and the ethical object is predominant, truth must be considered more in reference to art than science, if, that is, unity is to be preserved in the work generally."', '"Work,Science,Truth"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403116', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', '"No God without a world, and no world without God."', '"God,World,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403117', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1d', '"Now the relation which, in the sphere of nature, being and semblance or sensation bear to one another in this antithesis, is the same as that which in ethics exists between good and pleasure or feeling."', '"Nature,Good,Ethics"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403118', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', '"The freedom to express yourself without fear - that perhaps is something we in the U.S. take for granted. It\'s almost inconceivable to think we would be afraid to express our opinions or thoughts, but that\'s not true for all parts of the world now, and certainly not before World War II."', '"War,Freedom,Fear"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403119', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', '"The accounting of the sacrifice is, more than anything else, the attitude toward war memorials in our time."', '"Attitude,War,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403120', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', 'I really feel that my life story is a continuation of the Great American Dream - the immigrant who comes to this country and is allowed to excel. How many other countries would let me do that?', '"Life,Great,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403121', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', '"I remember saying that wars must not be glorified, but wars must be remembered."', '"Remember,Saying,Remembered"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403122', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', '"I think it is fair to say that during World War II there was a high sense of purpose. The country had a very clear vision of its own standing, of its own morality. It was not an ambiguous time. Today, we live in a world that is highly ambiguous, very fractured, with many of the historical, traditional values in a state of collapse, really."', '"War,Time,Today"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403123', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff1e', 'I was born in an enemy country. Only in America can someone who came from that beginning do what I am doing. It would never happen in Germany or Japan.', '"I Am,America,Beginning"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403124', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff21', '"Phase contrast was not discovered while working with a microscope, but in a different part of optics."', '"Microscope,Phase,Contrast"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403125', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff21', '"How quick are we to learn: that is, to imitate what others have done or thought before. And how slow to understand: that is, to see the deeper connections."', '"Done,See,Slow"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403126', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff21', '"With the phase-contrast method still in the first somewhat primitive stage, I went in 1932 to the Zeiss Works in Jena to demonstrate. It was not received with such enthusiasm as I had expected."', '"Stage,Enthusiasm,First"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403127', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff21', '"About 1930, our laboratory had obtained a large concave grating and set it up in a Runge-Paschen mounting."', '"Laboratory,Up,About"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403128', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff22', '"The Swedish Academy of Sciences has seen fit, by awarding the Nobel Prize, to honour the method of producing ammonia from nitrogen and hydrogen."', '"Seen,Prize,Academy"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403129', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff22', 'Gaseous nitrogen combines with gaseous hydrogen in simple quantitative proportions to produce gaseous ammonia.', '"Simple,Quantitative,Hydrogen"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403130', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff22', '"Under natural conditions, the soil does not lose its fixed nitrogen."', '"Lose,Soil,Natural"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403131', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff22', 'Agricultural husbandry essentially maintains the balance of bound nitrogen.', '"Balance,Bound,Nitrogen"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403132', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff23', '"I\'m truly worried about the country\'s direction. I can tell you this categorically, we\'ve got the weakest president and the weakest governor in the history of my 50 years of public service."', '"History,Service,Direction"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403133', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff23', '"I don\'t want to rust out, I\'d rather wear out."', '"Rust,Wear,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403134', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', 'Genius is an overused word. The world has known only about a half dozen geniuses. I got only fairly near.', '"World,Genius,Half"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403135', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"Suddenly, at about ten o\'clock, a dull thud sounded somewhere far away from us, and simultaneously we saw a small white round cloud about half a mile ahead of us where the shrapnel had exploded. The battle had begun."', '"Battle,White,Ahead"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403136', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"Signs of fatigue soon manifested themselves more and more strongly, and slowly the men dropped out one by one, from sheer exhaustion. No murmur of complaint, however, would be heard."', '"Men,More,Signs"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403137', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"Life that only a few hours before had glowed with enthusiasm and exultation, suddenly paled and sickened."', '"Life,Enthusiasm,Only"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403138', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"IN trying to recall my impressions during my short war duty as an officer in the Austrian Army, I find that my recollections of this period are very uneven and confused."', '"War,Duty,Confused"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403139', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"One gets into a strange psychological, almost hypnotic, state of mind while on the firing line which probably prevents the mind\'s eye from observing and noticing things in a normal way."', '"Mind,Way,Strange"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403140', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"The outbreak of the war found my wife and me in Switzerland, where we were taking a cure."', '"War,Wife,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403141', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"Although I had resigned my commission as an officer two years before, I immediately left Switzerland, accompanied by my wife, in order to report for duty. As it happened, a wire reached me a day later calling me to the colors."', '"Wife,Colors,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403142', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"What impressed me particularly in Vienna was the strict order everywhere. No mob disturbances of any kind, in spite of the greatly increased liberty and relaxation of police regulations."', '"Me,Police,Liberty"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403143', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"My wife volunteered her services as Red Cross nurse, insisting upon being sent to the front, in order to be as near me as could be, but it developed later that no nurse was allowed to go farther than the large troop hospitals far in the rear of the actual operations."', '"Wife,Me,Red"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403144', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"The moral effect of the thundering of one\'s own artillery is most extraordinary, and many of us thought that we had never heard any more welcome sound than the deep roaring and crashing that started in at our rear."', '"Welcome,Never,Extraordinary"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403145', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"We started at once to dig our trenches, half of my platoon stepping forward abreast, the men being placed an arm\'s length apart. After laying their rifles down, barrels pointing to the enemy, a line was drawn behind the row of rifles and parallel to it."', '"Men,Enemy,Down"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403146', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"Human nerves quickly get accustomed to the most unusual conditions and circumstances and I noticed that quite a number of men actually fell asleep from sheer exhaustion in the trenches, in spite of the roaring of the cannon about us and the whizzing of shrapnel over our heads."', '"Men,Circumstances,Human"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403147', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff24', '"I saw a great many men die afterwards, some suffering horribly, but I do not recall any death that affected me quite so much as that of this first victim in my platoon."', '"Death,Men,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403148', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"For me, cinema is a vice. I love it intimately."', '"Love,Me,Cinema"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403149', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"I am profoundly fascinated by cruelty, fear, horror and death. My films show my preoccupation with violence, the pathology of violence."', '"Death,Fear,I Am"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403150', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"Cinemascope is not for men, but for snakes and funerals."', '"Men,Snakes,Funerals"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403151', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"I like folk songs, but ten horses couldn\'t bring me to a concert or an opera."', '"Me,Opera,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403152', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', 'Each picture has some sort of rhythm which only the director can give it. He has to be like the captain of a ship.', '"Picture,Captain,Ship"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403153', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', 'My private life has nothing to do with my films.', '"Life,Private Life,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403154', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', 'I am not an artist. I am a craftsman.', '"I Am,Artist,Craftsman"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403155', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"You cannot make a social-conscious picture in which you say that the intermediary between the hand and the brain is the heart. I mean, that\'s a fairy tale - definitely."', '"Heart,Brain,Picture"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403156', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"In America, sex is preached; in France, it is done."', '"Sex,America,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403157', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"Music is the same to me as it was to Goethe - a pleasant noise. I am an eye man, not an ear man."', '"Music,Man,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403158', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', 'Women have always been my best friends.', '"Best,Women,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403159', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', 'I do not like producers.', '"Like,Producers"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403160', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"It is just that all my life I have been so involved in my work that I guess one could say in general that, whenever I had to balance my private life and my profession, my profession always won out."', '"Life,Work,Balance"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403161', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"I was something that is always hated in Hollywood - a perfectionist; nobody likes a perfectionist, you know."', '"Nobody,Know,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403162', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff25', '"I was called the greatest director in Europe, but I was just a hard worker."', '"Hard,Europe,Just"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403163', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff26', '"I am not in this world to live up to other people\'s expectations, nor do I feel that the world must live up to mine."', '"World,I Am,Expectations"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403164', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff26', '"Our dependency makes slaves out of us, especially if this dependency is a dependency of our self-esteem. If you need encouragement, praise, pats on the back from everybody, then you make everybody your judge."', '"Praise,Back,Judge"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403165', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff27', 'We need art more than ever as we stagger toward the Millennium.', '"Art,More,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403166', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff27', 'I give thanks everyday that I\'ve been able to take my craziness and make it work for me.', '"Work,Me,Thanks"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403167', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff28', '"She had in mind a different kind of looking person, because his appearance is not at all like mine."', '"Mind,Looking,Appearance"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403168', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff28', 'The performance of a lifetime is the perfect thing to be doing at this age because I can use the age.', '"Age,Perfect,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403169', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', 'Major actions by courageous and wise men will be necessary to avoid our continuing to blunder into the space age like unenlightened and selfish idiots.', '"Space,Age,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403170', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"The universe is so unique and perfect that it could not have originated by chance but was divined by flawless, creative design."', '"Chance,Design,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403171', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"I have a good idea every two years. Give me a topic, I will give you the idea!"', '"Good,Me,Will"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403172', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"If many things in the past have gone wrong in the lives of men and in the lives of their communities, it is because both small- and large-scale activities were blundered into without any thought or vision of universal planning."', '"Men,Vision,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403173', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', 'I soon became convinced... that all the theorizing would be empty brain exercise and therefore a waste of time unless one first ascertained what the population of the universe really consists of.', '"Time,Brain,Exercise"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403174', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"Every evening, I come home tired and have just enough energy to fill out the endless tax forms, to pay bills, not to let my house neglected and to hear the radio concert for an hour."', '"Home,Evening,Tired"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403175', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"Mountains were once my big adventure but is is over since a long time; I still dream from the wonderful days sometimes, read also a few pages from a mountain book. But the thought of doing again active mountain climbing has faded."', '"Time,Long,Long Time"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403176', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"Jupiter is so big and its gravitational pull so strong that man would find it difficult to move about on the surface. The answer is to whittle it down to proper size with terrajets and nuclear power, using the debris to increase the size of Jupiter\'s moons so they, too, can be colonized."', '"Power,Man,Difficult"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403177', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff29', '"Astronautics, strictly speaking, will be concerned with voyages to other stars. Remarkably enough, to achieve such feats, we might not even have to leave the earth. It would suffice to accelerate the sun itself to a very high speed and let it drag all its planets with it."', '"Stars,Sun,Earth"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403178', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', 'Diversification and globalization are the keys to the future.', '"Future,Globalization,Diversification"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403179', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', '"In the 1970s, Japan moved into the U.S. turf with its televisions, cars, chips, and steel. But if you think about it, the only business Japan destroyed was the U.S. television industry."', '"Business,Television,Steel"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403180', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', '"Whatever the trend in exchange rates or whatever the external factors, a manufacturing company is always faced with the mission of transforming itself into a company that can produce higher value-added to absorb the increase in the cost of living in the country it\'s operating in."', '"Country,Mission,Company"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403181', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', '"Japanese tend to put sales and market share first. They make many products with the aim of raising sales. But then profits decline, and companies find themselves falling into debt... I changed the mindset at Canon by getting people to realize that profits come first."', '"Aim,People,Falling"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403182', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', '"Canon is basically a very aggressive company. Our company works on competitive principles. It does not treat people equally, but it does treat them fairly."', '"Treat,People,Aggressive"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403183', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2b', '"The world is facing a new networked, digital lifestyle, and we will ensure that Canon remains ahead of the game."', '"World,Game,New"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403184', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', 'Jealousy is the tribute mediocrity pays to genius.', '"Jealousy,Genius,Mediocrity"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403185', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', 'Hearing nuns\' confessions is like being stoned to death with popcorn.', '"Death,Like,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403186', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', 'Show me your hands. Do they have scars from giving? Show me your feet. Are they wounded in service? Show me your heart. Have you left a place for divine love?', '"Inspirational,Love,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403187', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', 'Pride is an admission of weakness; it secretly fears all competition and dreads all rivals.', '"Pride,Competition,Weakness"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403188', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', 'Love is a mutual self-giving which ends in self-recovery.', '"Love,Love Is,Mutual"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403189', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', '"The big print giveth, and the fine print taketh away."', '"Big,Fine,Away"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403190', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', '"Life is like a cash register, in that every account, every thought, every deed, like every sale, is registered and recorded."', '"Life,Cash,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403191', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', '"The proud man counts his newspaper clippings, the humble man his blessings."', '"Humble,Man,Blessings"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403192', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', '"Baloney is flattery laid on so thick it cannot be true, and blarney is flattery so thin we love it."', '"Love,True,Flattery"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403193', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2c', '"I feel it is time that I also pay tribute to my four writers, Matthew, Mark, Luke and John."', '"Time,Feel,Four"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403194', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2d', 'We crucify ourselves between two thieves: regret for yesterday and fear of tomorrow.', '"Fear,Regret,Tomorrow"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403195', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2d', 'Many of us crucify ourselves between two thieves - regret for the past and fear of the future.', '"Future,Fear,Regret"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403196', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2d', '"In this one book are the two most interesting personalities in the whole world - God and yourself. The Bible is the story of God and man, a love story in which you and I must write our own ending, our unfinished autobiography of the creature and the Creator."', '"Love,God,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403197', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"Living with only the bare essentials has not only provided superficial benefits such as the pleasure of a tidy room or the simple ease of cleaning, it has also led to a more fundamental shift. It\'s given me a chance to think about what it really means to be happy."', '"Chance,Simple,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403198', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"Holding on to things from the past is the same as clinging to an image of yourself in the past. If you\'re the least bit interested in changing anything about yourself, I suggest you be brave and start letting things go."', '"Yourself,Brave,Past"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403199', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"Minimalism had to be born, not out of a mere spur-of-the-moment idea or yearning for a new lifestyle, but from an earnest desire and fervent need to rethink our lives."', '"New,Lifestyle,Born"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403200', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I wasn\'t always a minimalist. I used to buy a lot of things, believing that all those possessions would increase my self-worth and lead to a happier life. I loved collecting a lot of useless stuff, and I couldn\'t throw anything away."', '"Life,Useless,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403201', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'There\'s happiness in having less.', '"Happiness,Less,Having"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403202', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'Some of you may think that I\'m a loser: an unmarried adult with not much money. The old me would have been way too embarrassed to admit all this. I was filled with useless pride. But I honestly don\'t care about things like that any . The reason is very simple: I\'m perfectly happy just as I am.', '"Money,Pride,Simple"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403203', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"If you ask me what minimalism is really about, I would say that it\'s the altering of values - enter the small doors of minimalism and come out on the other side with big ideas."', '"Me,Ideas,Doors"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403204', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I used to pretend to be an expert on various kinds of music, even if they didn\'t really interest me."', '"Music,Me,Expert"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403205', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'I used to like taking pictures. I wanted to capture precious moments and make them mine. I wanted to hang on to everything that might someday become a fond memory.', '"Memory,Precious,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403206', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'Unhappiness isn\'t just the result of genetics or past trauma or career trouble. I think that some of our unhappiness is simply due to the burden of all our things.', '"Past,Result,Trauma"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403207', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"Spending less time on cleaning or shopping means I have more time to spend with friends, go out, or travel on my days off."', '"Time,Travel,Shopping"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403208', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"It\'s not as though you feel satisfied after collecting a certain amount of stuff. Instead, you keep thinking about what you\'re missing."', '"Thinking,Feel,Satisfied"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403209', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"To me, DIY means minimizing dependency on what others make for me."', '"Me,Others,Make"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403210', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I would say that if the idea of decluttering pushes some kind of a button in you, it may be a sign to give it a try."', '"Try,Say,May"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403211', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"The important thing is not the measurement of how many or few things you have, but your own state of mind and how you feel about the things you have and don\'t have."', '"Mind,Feel,Important"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403212', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'Traditional paintings have few figures in them and value negative space. Japanese calligraphy and brush paintings are in black and white. Haiku is the shortest poem form in the world. These are a few examples of a minimalistic aesthetic in Japanese art and culture.', '"Space,Art,Black And White"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403213', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"We think that the more we have, the happier we will be. We never know what tomorrow might bring, so we collect and save as much as we can. This means we need a lot of money, so we gradually start judging people by how much money they have."', '"Money,Tomorrow,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403214', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"Whether we live alone or with other people, few acknowledge the presence of another roommate. This roommate is named \'Things\' and the space that \'Things\' occupies is typically a lot larger than the space people have for themselves."', '"Alone,Space,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403215', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'I want to create my own living space and grow my own food instead of paying someone to supply those for me.', '"Space,Food,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403216', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"In my community of minimalists, there are really wealthy people who work at stock brokerage firms, there are people who are unemployed, but it doesn\'t seem to matter. We\'re all really good friends, and we get along really well. It\'s a very varied and diverse community."', '"Work,Good,Community"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403217', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I think that \'minimalist\' is a useful label for other people to identify me, but from my standpoint, I doesn\'t necessarily have an identity as that."', '"Me,People,Identity"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403218', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I actually think that the more something is important to you, the more it\'s OK to actually let it go."', '"Important,Go,More"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403219', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"I enjoy challenging myself to try new things, going outdoors, scuba diving, running a marathon. Anything that I have never done before, I enjoy trying it out."', '"Myself,New,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403220', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', '"There are more things to gain from eliminating excess than you might imagine: time, space, freedom, and energy, for example."', '"Freedom,Space,Time"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403221', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'You can\'t help but fixate on something that you\'re about to throw away because it\'s right in front of you.', '"Help,Right,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403222', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2e', 'We think we can\'t become a minimalist until our lives have settled down. But it\'s actually the other way around; we won\'t be able to settle down until we\'re living a minimalist life.', '"Life,Way,Living"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403223', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I ain\'t giving up on myself, so if you give up on me, I ain\'t got nothing else to say for you."', '"Myself,Me,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403224', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I know I haven\'t always done things the right way. I\'m just trying to reflect on how to make myself better, how to become a better man, a better father, a better person, a better artist."', '"Myself,Man,Father"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403225', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'You got one life to live. So I\'m living it the way I want to live it.', '"Life,Way,Live"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403226', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'You gotta catch the sauce. Move with me... I\'m dripping sauce.', '"Me,Catch,Dripping"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403227', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I do everything for my family.', '"Family,Everything"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403228', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'ve always been into fashion since I was a kid. I love fashion. I appreciate it. I just enjoy dressing up and getting all the new sneakers and all the hot exclusive clothes - I did even when I was young.', '"Love,Hot,New"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403229', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Jupiter, Pluto, pick a planet: we can go there. I just got a bit more work to do in the music industry, and we\'re going to space, baby."', '"Work,Space,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403230', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Every mistake you make allows you to be honest because what\'s in the dark will come to light, so it\'s better to be truthful about it."', '"Light,Mistake,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403231', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to keep doing what I\'m doing and see how far I can go. See when it stops. See what the end is like. I want to make this moment last as long as I can make it. If I miss a day, I\'m afraid I\'ll miss out on a smash record."', '"Moment,Long,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403232', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Don\'t matter if you\'re rich, poor or whatever, you just want to be able to have your own experiences in life and listen and learn from other people."', '"Life,Rich,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403233', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I like all types of women. I accept them as they are when they come into my life... But I\'m not a romantic. I\'m just up-front. I like to be a part of something real, not make-believe. I tell women to tell me the truth, to just lay it out. Let me be the judge and decide if I want you around or not. Let me have my choice."', '"Life,Truth,Women"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403234', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My music is like a diary. I use every experience.', '"Experience,Music,Diary"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403235', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'ll always keep you guessing. I\'m living up to the name. It\'s powerful. That\'s just what I do.', '"Name,Living,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403236', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I feel like I just wanna go back to being more underground.', '"Feel,Back,Go"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403237', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Don\'t ask for a million dollars. Ask for the stuff that\'ll get you a million dollars - your health, your brain, your sanity, wisdom. Prepare me for when I do get that million. Make sure I don\'t go crazy, make sure I help my family."', '"Wisdom,Family,Health"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403238', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"If you\'re doing what you think people might like, rather than doing what you like, people will see through it."', '"People,Will,See"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403239', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My favorite designer has to be Louis Vuitton.', '"Favorite,Designer,Louis"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403240', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m always a fan of good business moves.', '"Business,Good,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403241', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I feel like guitar explains a lot. You can just listen to a guitar without any lyrics over it; you can just feel what kind of track it is. If it\'s pain... you can feel it. It sets the mood.', '"Pain,Guitar,Mood"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403242', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I gotta have my long trench coats, a nice scarf for the winter time when you\'re walking around, and some nice fitted jeans to go with the trench coats."', '"Time,Long,Walking"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403243', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Jimi Hendrix, he was a rock star. But he played guitar; I don\'t. I\'ve just found ways to use words to make my mark in this history book."', '"History,Guitar,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403244', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m not for the publicity stunts. Leave my son out of the publicity stunts.', '"Son,Leave,Stunts"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403245', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"You got to make the most of your second life. I was born Nayvadius, but now I\'m Future. Should I dwell on what Nayvadius was supposed to be? I get a chance to experience life as something else. I wasn\'t supposed to be like this."', '"Life,Future,Experience"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403246', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Rihanna takes risks, and I love a woman who takes risks. It just goes to show you have your own mind and your own way of thinking."', '"Love,Thinking,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403247', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I don\'t read blogs. I\'m living the life they\'re writing about. So why read about it?', '"Life,Living,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403248', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I just want to be an inspiration. I\'m a rock star, I\'m Future Hendrix."', '"Future,Rock Star,Rock"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403249', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I can\'t leave home without certain movies. \'The Godfather\' is a big one for me. And I\'ve gotta have my beats so I can write new music.', '"Home,Music,Movies"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403250', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I take a little bit from everybody and add that to my life to make me, me. I wanna be nobody else but Future. When you look at me, I want you to say, \'Future.\' The way I talk, the way I dress, there\'s nobody in the world but me."', '"Life,Future,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403251', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m not just a hip-hop artist; I feel like I\'m a rock star.', '"Feel,Rock Star,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403252', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Every day, I bring out something new. You got to be prepared - you got to have a few outfits laying out for when you wake up, in case you want to change, to set the mood."', '"Change,Day,Mood"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403253', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"My kids gotta understand: they gotta make a sacrifice, having a superstar dad."', '"Dad,Sacrifice,Understand"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403254', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I was shy talking about certain things, and I was shy with being honest because I didn\'t want people to judge me talking about fatherhood and how somebody should have my child around me."', '"Me,People,Shy"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403255', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"The weirdest place I ever actually woke up in was a villa on the beach in Mexico. It was burning hot, and there were all these crabs walking around me. But I was feeling good, so I went with the vibe."', '"Good,Me,Hot"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403256', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Man, I wanna be there for everybody. I wanna make everybody happy, and I can\'t... That\'s why I stay in the studio."', '"Man,Happy,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403257', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"You get inspiration from craziest places. It\'s just about being creative. You gotta step outside that box, you know what I\'m saying, to reach the people. You never know who can feel it; who it can connect to."', '"Step,Feel,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403258', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I feel like guys, girls, whatever it is, you just come out hoping to make the best record. You just try to have a conversation and just create what you\'ve talked about. Whatever you find to fit the beat at the time, what the person is down for, wherever the beat takes you towards."', '"Best,Time,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403259', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I don\'t even talk about being locked up in any of my songs.', '"Talk,Up,About"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403260', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"For just being a black artist in rock n\' roll and be able to step outside and create, and make great music. And just be different. Just a different breed. And that\'s what I love about Jimi Hendrix\'s music - the way he plays the guitar is so different. He\'s just an icon all around."', '"Love,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403261', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"The hardest part of fame and success is adapting to the people around you that\'s changing. It changes the way people look at you from how they used to look at you. They listen to you on the radio, they look at you on TV and when people speak on you in a good light, you have a couple people who hold grudges."', '"Success,Good,Look"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403262', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"You make music to change the radio, not make music for the radio."', '"Change,Music,Radio"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403263', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I was probably 15 when I started going to the studio with the older cats in my neighborhood. They heard me rap outside one time; I was just freestyling. And they invited me to the studio. It\'s good when you\'re accepted, no matter what crowd. That\'s the first step of believing you can do whatever you feel like putting your mind to."', '"Time,Good,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403264', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want that longevity in the career, so if you don\'t know how to get it, you trying to chase that high, you trying to continue to chase your dreams and conquer things you never thought you could get. And you just want to get there too soon, so you taking the wrong moves to try and compensate what\'s not happening."', '"Dreams,Your Dreams,Conquer"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403265', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I have a crazy work ethic. I\'ll do 20 songs a day. I love music that much.', '"Love,Work,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403266', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I\'m always most comfortable in the studio. It\'s my comfort zone. I love being there, and I love making records."', '"Love,Comfort,Always"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403267', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My daddy didn\'t even sign my birth certificate. So I ain\'t never had his last name.', '"Name,Never,Birth"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403268', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Rumours are rumours. The Internet is going to report whatever they have to speculate on.', '"Internet,Whatever,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403269', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"For me, it\'s always been one of my pet peeves to keep people engaged and talking, and just always being interested in what I have going on. To keep the level of creativity always turned up to the max."', '"Pet,Me,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403270', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"You want to create your own path, no matter what situation you\'re in."', '"Path,Situation,Create"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403271', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"That\'s the time that I enjoy: away from the cameras, away from the audience, the scenery of going out to eat and everybody\'s staring at me."', '"Time,Scenery,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403272', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m not trying to feed off of a concept that another artist had - that\'s not what I do.', '"Trying,Artist,Feed"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403273', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Sometimes it\'s hard to open up about your personal life, your relationship because you always want the music to be in the forefront. You want the music to be the biggest carrier of everything that you represent."', '"Life,Relationship,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403274', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I just enjoy dressing up and getting all the new sneakers and all the hot exclusive clothes - I did even when I was young.', '"Hot,New,Young"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403275', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I was drawn to love songs, but I was just drawn to great music - no matter if it\'s hip-hop, pop, R&B or whether it\'s rock n\' roll or country. It could be a Garth Brooks song, and if it\'s a smash, then I\'ll love the different wordplay and different melodies. That\'s what I\'m a fan of - great music."', '"Love,Music,Great"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403276', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When I first used Auto-Tune, I never used it to sing. I wasn\'t using it the way T-Pain was. I used it to rap because it makes my voice sound grittier."', '"Way,Voice,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403277', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to have bosses around me, \'cause at the end of the day, 10 years from now, 20 years from now, you want to make relationships to keep \'em, you know what I\'m saying. So I make my relationships to keep \'em - all my relationships - not try to burn bridges that you may need to cross over one day."', '"End Of The Day,Me,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403278', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'You don\'t question magic.', '"Magic,Question,You"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403279', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"My kids need to be around me. And the times that I\'m out of town, if I\'m not too busy, they can come to me."', '"Busy,Me,Need"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403280', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My day one fans - my fans from my mix tape days - know my life now. They know where I\'ve been. You don\'t want to have a disconnection with those fans. You have to give them all of you because they feel like they\'ve known you.', '"Life,My Life,Day"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403281', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Jay Z wasn\'t great when 2pac and Biggie was alive.', '"Great,Alive,Biggie"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403282', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"G-Rock from the Westside, from Allen Temple. He gave my name, The Future; he was like, \'Man, you the future.\' Just stuck with the name."', '"Future,Man,Temple"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403283', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When you grow up in something, you don\'t even know if it\'s bad or good. You just know that\'s how it is."', '"Good,Grow,Bad"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403284', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"The most calmest place I can be is the studio. And like, I stay in there \'cause I know, when I come out, it\'s back to reality. Man, if you\'re angry all day, man, stay in the studio."', '"Angry,Reality,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403285', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'The most fun moments are being on the stage and seeing how the crowd reacts to your music. The energy of the crowd that makes you just want to go in and keep doing it and be a part of this forever.', '"Music,Energy,Fun"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403286', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"That\'s that Dungeon Family ethos: being able to reinvent yourself, stand out and stand alone. Having your own character and having your own image, no matter what they say about you. I want to show my versatility and how diverse I am, how I approach the track, my rhythm, my melodies. It\'s something different."', '"Alone,Family,Character"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403287', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to give the music attention and be in the studio. I want to give all my attention to my music, my kids, my family, so I just wanna focus on certain things besides social media."', '"Family,Music,Focus"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403288', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I feel like I\'m doing something in Atlanta that nobody ever did as far as rap. If it happens to end up on the top 40 or the pop charts, it doesn\'t mean I meant to go pop. It\'s just where the music took me. It started at the bottom, and it rises."', '"Music,Me,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403289', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I like to express myself through the clothes that I wear.', '"Myself,Clothes,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403290', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Where I know I wanna go is being consistent on business, and that\'s just making another artist, my clothing line - capitalizing off the moment. I wanna be consistently doing that - capitalizing off every move I make."', '"Business,Moment,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403291', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I don\'t take anything for granted. I know there are a million and one dudes who are rapping, wishing they were in my shoes."', '"Shoes,Know,Anything"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403292', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"At first, Hendrix went and became a superstar in London, but if he walked past the Apollo in Harlem, no one would know who he was. I\'m the hip-hop version of him."', '"Past,Know,Hip-Hop"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403293', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When you\'re riding with your mom, and you\'re a kid, you\'d listen to \'Dear Mama\' and the radio friendly records. I used to sneak and listen to Too $hort."', '"Mom,Mama,Riding"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403294', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"At times, I think, \'What would I rather be doing than music?\' That\'s what you have to ask yourself, if you feel like you need to be somewhere else... But there\'s nothing else I want to do more than music. That\'s why I stay in the booth."', '"Music,Yourself,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403295', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Future\'s not everybody. The people who are taking my style are like my babies. I\'ve got a tribe of kids that want to be like me... But I understand why people want to imitate the things I do. They\'re dope. It comes naturally to me. My fans can expect greatness. If I wasn\'t me, I would want to be me."', '"Future,Me,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403296', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to judge the nannies that\'s around my child. I don\'t want to pay for a nanny that I never met, that I never got a chance to interview. That\'s not the life I want for my child. I want to be involved 100 percent in all decisions made. This my flesh and blood."', '"Life,Chance,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403297', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"My favorite rappers are, I can\'t really say. I like Kanye because he\'s so creative. He\'ll just do anything. I like what Kanye\'s bringing to the game. Lil Wayne. I like Wayne."', '"Game,Anything,Because"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403298', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'All gigs are good gigs. There\'s never a bad one. Everything have a reason behind it; you just got to find that reason.', '"Good,Bad,Never"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403299', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I\'m putting everything on the line in being able to express myself in a different way than rappers normally do. They might say, \'It\'s rap\' or \'It\'s R&B,\' but I\'m stepping outside the box and making music for me and making music for the fans to understand me. I\'m going the extra distance to be able to come across different."', '"Music,Myself,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403300', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"If I told a lie, then I got to come back and correct it years later. I hate that I have to be the person that touch on their life and be personal and be direct with certain situations, but man, I\'m glad that it\'s me than them."', '"Life,Hate,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403301', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I don\'t just write hits for myself, or for other artists, or to just be writing it. I write it because I was born to do this. I was given this gift, and I\'m making the most of my opportunity."', '"Myself,Opportunity,Gift"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403302', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I love \'Troy.\' I love Brad Pitt\'s character - when he went to Troy, he just ran over it. Then this particular scene where they made this big old horse or something out of wood, and they hid inside the wood."', '"Love,Character,Big"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403303', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Everybody can relate to being real or true. Somehow, someway, you want to be real and true."', '"True,Real,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403304', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"\'I Won\' is not a love song. It\'s just me uplifting women in general. I\'m giving women the power to treat themselves as a trophy - to show that and know it in yourself and be confident - because when they do that, whoever they\'re with is winning."', '"Love,Women,Power"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403305', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Everybody wanna be a super dad and the best dad ever, but sometimes, I\'m just realizing that I\'m not perfect."', '"Best,Dad,Not Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403306', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I\'m just really a free spirit. You gotta be like that. \'Cause life ain\'t that complicated. It\'s only that complicated when you make it that way. I just wanna wake up and move with the way it goes. If it\'s meant to happen, it will happen."', '"Life,Free,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403307', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I know melody. I know rhythm; I know bass guitar; I know the piano. I know everything about music that helps build the music that go along with creating the whole art form, you know what I\'m saying?"', '"Art,Music,Guitar"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403308', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to let little kids know that no matter what situation they come up in, that they\'re not exempt from success. All I ever wanted was for people to believe in me and just recognize my potential. I came, I struggled, I made it, I conquered."', '"Success,Me,Believe"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403309', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"If you behind me, I\'m not going to look back and try and figure out what you\'re doing behind me."', '"Look,Me,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403310', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"You have to just do music, and you\'re becoming this entertainer, and so many people require so much of your time for different things, different obligations you have to make money, or just different obligations you have as a person in whatever the situation may be."', '"Money,Time,Music"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403311', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"People think fashion shows take hours - it\'s 15 minutes. You walk in, do red carpet, take the pictures, you sit down... and then it\'s over."', '"Walk,People,Red"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403312', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Even if it comes off natural, everyone has a fashion sense."', '"Fashion,Everyone,Sense"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403313', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I feel a responsibility for telling the truth.', '"Truth,Responsibility,Feel"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403314', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'ve always been into fashion since I was a kid. I love fashion. I appreciate it.', '"Love,Always,Fashion"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403315', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"It\'s hard to get burned out or uninspired, man."', '"Man,Hard,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403316', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"The melodies I come up with, they\'re not normal."', '"Normal,Up,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403317', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m the top rapper in the world.', '"World,Top,Rapper"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403318', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want people to say, \'He evolved throughout his whole career.\' I wanna be able to have the most number one records ever. The most Top 10 records ever."', '"People,Want,Top"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403319', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'It takes an astronaut so long to get to space - that\'s how long it takes to catch up on my music.', '"Space,Music,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403320', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"In Atlanta, there\'s no limitation to where you can take your music. You can be as creative as you want to be."', '"Music,Your,Want"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403321', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'You know that I can make hits. You know I can do all these rap records.', '"Know,I Can,Rap"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403322', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Big Rube was on my first album and some of my mixtapes. His words are so powerful. I want to speak every word he says into existence. I wanna be a part of that! I wanna be a part of greatness. His wordplay is great to me.', '"Great,Me,Words"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403323', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to be the most melodic artist. \'His music ability, the way he write, his creativity is undeniable.\' I want people to say that about me."', '"Music,Me,Creativity"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403324', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"It takes compromise to raise a child, especially with a schedule like mine."', '"Compromise,Mine,Child"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403325', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My style is a part of my music. You can\'t be an artist and not put any thought or effort into the way you appear.', '"Music,Effort,Style"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403326', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I never get starstruck.', '"Never,Get"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403327', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I wanna make my imprint in the game as far as music - hip-hop, and just music, period. \'Cause I come from hip-hop, that\'s my background, but I\'m not gonna let that limit me from where I can go."', '"Music,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403328', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My obsession with outer space is my way of being different. I make astronaut music. It takes an astronaut so long to get to space - that\'s how long it takes to catch up on my music.', '"Space,Music,Long"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403329', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I wouldn\'t say I\'m underrated, but more reserved. Only time will tell, but I\'ve been good so far in being consistent and making hit after hit writing for myself and other artists, from rap to R&B, and being able to make those different records."', '"Time,Good,Myself"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403330', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I need to let people know who I am and instead of just trying to make great records, just be honest and make it more personal and make it more passionate, to make records with emotion and not be afraid to express that."', '"Great,I Am,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403331', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My three wishes are just be respected out the game. I want respect from everybody. And just make a successful clothing line and company. I\'m not going to put a number on it. Just to have a great career.', '"Respect,Great,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403332', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I\'ve made a lot of mistakes in my life. I wouldn\'t say musically, though."', '"Life,My Life,Mistakes"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403333', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Just wanna have plaques on plaques. That\'s what we goin\' for.', '"Just,Wanna,Goin"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403334', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"If I\'m the biggest artist in the world, cool, but I want to just be me."', '"Cool,Me,World"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403335', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I want my money to be different. I\'m not trying to have rapper money. My goal is to be able to get everything from the world that I can get.', '"Money,World,Trying"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403336', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I\'m just not going to settle for anything, you know?"', '"Know,Anything,Settle"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403337', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Just understand that the type of music that I make is something special.', '"Music,Understand,Special"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403338', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I just like being versatile, giving new styles and being creative."', '"New,Giving,Creative"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403339', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"All I know is record, record, record, record."', '"Know,Record"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403340', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I have to go places beyond music.', '"Music,Go,Beyond"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403341', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"My sister wants a Rollie. When I buy one now, I gotta buy like five, ten. It\'s crazy."', '"Crazy,Buy,Sister"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403342', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I try to look cool. I strategize. Sometimes it\'s like - that\'s part of the strategizing, to make it seem like I don\'t think about it."', '"Cool,Look,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403343', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"It\'s about being creative and drawing on who you are when you wake up, and expressing yourself through fashion."', '"Yourself,Drawing,Wake Up"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403344', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Man, I love being a dad. It\'s super fun."', '"Love,Dad,Man"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403345', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'It don\'t matter who I\'m working with. I just feel like I want to make the best record possible.', '"Best,Feel,Matter"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403346', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"My career choice is my career choice. Just stepping out of that zone, to be able to be a provider. I understand my position as a provider and my role as a dad also... Just being able to be comfortable with it."', '"Dad,Choice,Comfortable"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403347', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When I\'m in the studio, I stay in the studio, like, sometimes 20 hours out the day."', '"Day,Sometimes,Stay"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403348', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m an entrepreneur. This is my life. This my career. This the way I eat.', '"Life,My Life,Way"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403349', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When you\'re a man, you want to make decisions for your family, and sometimes the lady doesn\'t see what you see."', '"Family,Man,Lady"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403350', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"I want to show my versatility and how diverse I am, how I approach the track, my rhythm, my melodies. It\'s something different. Sometimes, the things I do haven\'t ever been done."', '"I Am,Sometimes,Done"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403351', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"At the end of the day, I\'m out of here - above anything."', '"End Of The Day,Day,End"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403352', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"The music I make, I\'m different."', '"Music,Make,Different"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403353', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"When you mix a record that someone else is on, you\'ve got to send it to them. They\'ve got to like the mix, you got to like the mix, the producer\'s got to like the mix. Too many people are involved!"', '"People,Someone,Like"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403354', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I\'m most comfortable when I\'m in the studio and music playing.', '"Music,Comfortable,Studio"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403355', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'Artists can most definitely control the culture of fashion. Kids and different fans look up to us for dressing pointers.', '"Culture,Look,Control"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403356', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'People respond to something melodic.', '"People,Respond,Something"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403357', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', '"Quality is everything to me, and I perfect everything I do."', '"Me,Quality,Perfect"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403358', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'My fashion sense is relatable but stands out because it\'s my own.', '"Fashion,My Own,Own"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403359', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff2f', 'I wanna be one of those special guys. Jimi Hendrix wasn\'t afraid of who he was. That\'s the part I emulate.', '"Afraid,Special,He"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403360', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"Life is not a bowl full of cherries, there\'s good and bad stuff."', '"Life,Good,Cherries"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403361', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'Vodka does not ease back pain. But it does get your mind off it.', '"Pain,Mind,Back"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403362', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'I have to make things right with Tiger first before anything else.', '"Tiger,Anything,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403363', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'A million thoughts went through my mind. What little mind I have.', '"Thoughts,Mind,Through"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403364', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"If the pressure is getting to you, whistle. In a barely audible way. It\'s the best way I know of to let go of tension. Music gets your mind off the situation, and the act of whistling melts the tension out of your body."', '"Best,Music,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403365', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'Every shot makes someone happy.', '"Happy,Someone,Shot"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403366', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'Golf isn\'t first on my list anymore. There are a lot of things ahead of golf and I have to go ahead and do those things so I can play golf. I\'m tired of hurting. Tired of fighting pain.', '"Pain,Tired,Fighting"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403367', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"When you play against the best, it brings the best out in everybody."', '"Best,Play,Against"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403368', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'Playing with friends is a victory.', '"Victory,Friends,Playing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403369', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"It\'s fun when the ball is going in the hole and things are going right, but it\'s a miserable game when things aren\'t going well."', '"Game,Fun,Right"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403370', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"The key factor in the vodka category is smoothness, and smoothness is what our vodka has."', '"Key,Category,Vodka"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403371', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"There is something magical about that green coat. I mean that sincerely. It\'s a very special week, and being able to wear that green jacket. It\'s made my whole career. It\'s special."', '"Green,Week,Special"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403372', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"A lot of amateurs are terrified of going up against a player who is clearly better than they are. They never play their best, because they aren\'t comfortable. There\'s one surefire way to get over that, and it\'s to ask yourself, \'What if I beat him?\' Imagine the possibility."', '"Best,Yourself,Better"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403373', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"When I hosted the dinner I served fast food hamburgers. It had nothing to do with black, white, purple, yellow, green race. it had nothing to do with Tiger or his family or his golf game."', '"Family,Food,Black"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403374', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'I realize I\'m not a machine. I\'m going to make mistakes.', '"Mistakes,Realize,Going"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403375', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'When things are going good they just keep going good.', '"Good,Keep Going,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403376', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'I\'ve been on the tour for 23 years and anybody who knows me knows that I am a jokester.', '"Me,I Am,Who"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403377', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"If I hadn\'t become a golfer, I doubt I\'d be wealthy, because I don\'t have the sort of ego that drives a person all day long. I might have wound up driving a tractor."', '"Long,Day,Ego"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403378', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"You would think that Freddy Couples-Nick Price would be the team to beat, but I\'ll tell you in skins, it\'s a matter of just hitting it at the right time."', '"Time,Matter,Beat"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403379', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"It was Jack\'s and Tom Watson\'s day yesterday. But today, it\'s another day."', '"Today,Day,Yesterday"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403380', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'Have a little fun. A few laughs.', '"Fun,Little,Few"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403381', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'I win everyday I\'m out there.', '"Win,Out,Everyday"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403382', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I might not come home with hardware, but I\'m winning."', '"Home,Winning,Come"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403383', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'They talk about Amen Corner but there\'s so much more to it than what meets the eye on this golf course.', '"Golf,Talk,Corner"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403384', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I wasn\'t sure I\'d ever win again. Every time I got close, somebody seemed to play a little better."', '"Time,Better,Win"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403385', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'It\'s nice to walk into a club and see your picture. Then you know you\'ve done something good.', '"Good,Walk,Picture"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403386', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"The greatest thing about golf, there\'s no end to it unless you\'re dead. You just go from here to the Senior Tour."', '"Dead,End,Golf"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403387', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"At the British Open, I had my opportunities, but the ball just didn\'t want to go in the hole on the back nine."', '"Back,Go,Ball"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403388', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"There\'s a lot of great people out here, I just appreciate it and hope everybody has had fun because I\'ve enjoyed my ride."', '"Hope,Great,Ride"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403389', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I think I can be competitive. Heck, anybody who can walk to the first tee here has a chance."', '"Chance,Walk,I Can"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403390', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I hope everybody\'s had fun, because I\'ve enjoyed my ride. I can tell you that. Now it\'s time to step aside and let some other young kid come in and win. Hopefully, they will, too."', '"Hope,Time,Ride"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403391', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"Every time I got close, somebody seemed to play a little better."', '"Time,Better,Play"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403392', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"When you have strings, everybody pulls you here and pulls you there."', '"Here,Strings,Everybody"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403393', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'I hate golf to be tricked up. To me it\'s a fun game.', '"Hate,Me,Game"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403394', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"Newspapers do a good job telling me what happened yesterday, but they\'d be a lot more impressive if they could tell me what\'s going to happen tomorrow."', '"Good,Tomorrow,Me"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403395', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I\'m glad I don\'t have to make a living farming. Too much hard work. Too many variables you don\'t have control over, like, is it going to rain? All I can say is, god bless the real farmers out there."', '"Work,God,Rain"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403396', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"Everybody saying you can\'t do this, you can\'t do that. I don\'t know why. Guess if you listen to it, you can convince yourself of it."', '"Yourself,Know,Why"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403397', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"It\'s kind of exciting again. I\'m doing everything right, right now. I\'m driving the ball well and I\'m hitting some pretty good irons and giving myself opportunities."', '"Good,Myself,Doing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403398', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', 'What\'s appropriate in America anymore?', '"America,Appropriate,Anymore"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403399', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff30', '"I\'m not a great player, but I\'m a damn good one."', '"Good,Great,Damn"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403400', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'To live without Hope is to Cease to live.', '"Hope,Live,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403401', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'Sarcasm: the last refuge of modest and chaste-souled people when the privacy of their soul is coarsely and intrusively invaded.', '"Soul,Privacy,People"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403402', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Power is given only to those who dare to lower themselves and pick it up. Only one thing matters, one thing; to be able to dare!"', '"Power,Dare,Matters"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403403', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"If there is no God, everything is permitted."', '"God,Everything,Permitted"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403404', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'The soul is healed by being with children.', '"Soul,Children,Being"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403405', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'The greatest happiness is to know the source of unhappiness.', '"Happiness,Great,Know"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403406', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"The cleverest of all, in my opinion, is the man who calls himself a fool at least once a month."', '"Man,Fool,Opinion"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403407', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"One can know a man from his laugh, and if you like a man\'s laugh before you know anything of him, you may confidently say that he is a good man."', '"Good,Man,Laugh"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403408', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Man is fond of counting his troubles, but he does not count his joys. If he counted them up as he ought to, he would see that every lot has enough happiness provided for it."', '"Happiness,Man,See"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403409', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'To love someone means to see him as God intended him.', '"Love,God,See"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403410', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"We sometimes encounter people, even perfect strangers, who begin to interest us at first sight, somehow suddenly, all at once, before a word has been spoken."', '"Perfect,People,Sometimes"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403411', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Beauty is mysterious as well as terrible. God and devil are fighting there, and the battlefield is the heart of man."', '"Beauty,God,Heart"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403412', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'Much unhappiness has come into the world because of bewilderment and things left unsaid.', '"World,Because,Things"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403413', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"There are things which a man is afraid to tell even to himself, and every decent man has a number of such things stored away in his mind."', '"Fear,Man,Mind"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403414', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Deprived of meaningful work, men and women lose their reason for existence; they go stark, raving mad."', '"Work,Women,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403415', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Happiness does not lie in happiness, but in the achievement of it."', '"Happiness,Achievement,Lie"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403416', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'Realists do not fear the results of their study.', '"Fear,Results,Study"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403417', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"It seems, in fact, as though the second half of a man\'s life is made up of nothing, but the habits he has accumulated during the first half."', '"Life,Man,Nothing"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403418', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"A real gentleman, even if he loses everything he owns, must show no emotion. Money must be so far beneath a gentleman that it is hardly worth troubling about."', '"Money,Gentleman,Real"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403419', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Men do not accept their prophets and slay them, but they love their martyrs and worship those whom they have tortured to death."', '"Love,Death,Men"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403420', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'The formula \'Two and two make five\' is not without its attractions.', '"Two,Five,Without"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403421', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Man only likes to count his troubles, but he does not count his joys."', '"Man,Only,He"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403422', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'It is not possible to eat me without insisting that I sing praises of my devourer?', '"Me,Possible,Eat"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403423', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', 'There is no subject so old that something new cannot be said about it.', '"New,Old,Cannot"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403424', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"Man, so long as he remains free, has no more constant and agonizing anxiety than find as quickly as possible someone to worship."', '"Man,Long,Free"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403425', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"If you were to destroy the belief in immortality in mankind, not only love but every living force on which the continuation of all life in the world depended, would dry up at once."', '"Life,Love,World"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00'),
	('403426', '6110d4a69c759c204c24ff31', '"A novel is a work of poetry. In order to write it, one must have tranquility of spirit and of impression."', '"Work,Poetry,Spirit"', '2023-05-29 12:13:00', '2023-05-29 12:13:00');